\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t b\u7915 ng t\u7881 nh t\u7915  trong gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng , trong l\'fac b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7841 nh \u273 \'e3 \u432 \u7899 t s\u361 ng \'e1o ng\u7911  b\u7857 ng v\u7843 i b\'f4ng, tr\'e1i tim v\u7851 n \u273 ang \u273 \u7853 p th\'ecnh th\u7883 ch, m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, nh\u432  nh\u7883 p tr\u7889 ng r\u7889 i lo\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u run r\u7849 y m\u7903  m\u7855 t, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y tia s\'e1ng \u273 \'e8n gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0u cam \u7845 m \'e1p, ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\u361 ng \u273 ang b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n s\'e1ng tr\u432 ng, l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 a tay s\u7901  m\u7863 t d\'e2y chuy\u7873 n b\u7857 ng ng\u7885 c \u273 eo tr\'ean c\u7893 , l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i \'e2m th\u7847 m d\'e3n ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u417  t\u7899 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\'fac c\'f2n \u273 ang h\u7885 c \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n c\u259 n ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  th\u7901 i \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, l\'fac \u7845 y m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903 , gi\u432 \u7901 ng tr\'ean b\'e0n d\u432 \u7899 i, trong ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 bu\u7891 ng v\u7879  sinh, ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m, ph\'f2ng \u273 \'e1nh r\u259 ng r\u7917 a m\u7863 t, toilet \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  trong h\'e0nh lang, c\'e1ch m\u7845 y ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  l\u7841 i x\'e2y m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u417  th\u7845 y m\'ecnh ra ngo\'e0i \u273 i nh\'e0 c\u7847 u, sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a, c\u7853 u ra s\u7913 c k\'eau to, \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a, nh\u432 ng b\'ean trong kh\'f4ng h\u7873  m\u7903 . C\u7853 u g\'e0o l\u7899 n t\'ean b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng, n\'f3i "T\u7899  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e2y, mau m\u7903  c\u7917 a", th\u7871  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng b\'ean trong, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec sao c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7901  m\u7901  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng b\'ean kia c\'e1nh c\u7917 a, c\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ba ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  trong \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng b\'ean trong c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t "Tr\'ec Di\'ean", "Tr\'ec Di\'ean" kia n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng n\'ean m\u7903  c\u7917 a, th\u7913  b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 \uc0\u273 \'e1m b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng s\u7899 m chi\u7873 u chung \u273 \u7909 ng v\u7899 i c\u7853 u l\u7841 i \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng chung m\u7897 t ch\u7895  v\u7899 i th\u7913  kia, \u273 em c\u7853 u nh\u7889 t \u7903  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\'ec Di\'ean" n\'fap sau l\uc0\u432 ng b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\u361 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, nh\u7871 ch m\'f4i, n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7915 ng t\u7881 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i theo ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a duy v\u7853 t, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 n\'f3i c\u7853 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng duy v\u7853 t. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c g\'ec kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng "\'c2m D\u432 \u417 ng Nh\'e3n" c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y qu\u7927  th\u7847 n nh\u432  ti\u7875 u thuy\u7871 t gi\u7843  t\u432 \u7903 ng tr\'ean TV mi\'eau t\u7843 , nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia. Ch\'fang r\'ecnh m\'f2 tr\'e1i ph\u7843 i, v\u7901 n quanh c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7847 y b\u7909 ng \'e1c \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng c\u7843 m \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y t\u7915  r\u7845 t s\u7899 m, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u s\u7907  h\'e3i, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i v\u7899 i ai, cho \u273 \u7871 n khi m\u432 \u7901 i tu\u7893 i n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7849 y xu\u7889 ng t\u7915  tr\'ean c\u7847 u thang trung t\'e2m th\u432 \u417 ng m\u7841 i, may m\'e0 kh\'f4ng x\u7843 y ra v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec l\u7899 n, h\u7879  th\u7889 ng gi\'e1m s\'e1t c\u7911 a trung t\'e2m th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i hi\u7875 n th\u7883  xung quanh c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\'e0 c\u7853 u t\u7921  m\'ecnh ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng. B\'e0 ngo\u7841 i v\'e0o vi\u7879 n ch\u259 m s\'f3c c\u7853 u, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o cho c\u7853 u ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n sau l\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t d\u7845 u b\'e0n tay h\u417 i nh\u7887  m\'e0u \u273 o\u777 , g\u7847 n nh\u432  nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 ngo\uc0\u7841 i qu\'e1 s\u7907  h\'e3i, b\u7845 y gi\u7901  m\u7899 i \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c n\'e0y, ng\'e0y \u273 \'eam t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u7903  ph\'f2ng b\u7879 nh tr\'f4ng coi c\u7853 u, ch\u7901  t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u chuy\u7875 n bi\u7871 n t\u7889 t li\u7873 n d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i b\'e1i ph\u7887 ng m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n r\u7845 t n\u7893 i danh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n nh\uc0\u7899  v\u7883  \u273 \u7841 o nh\'e2n \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nh\u7905  r\'f5 m\u7863 t kia bu\u7897 c m\u7897 t s\u7907 i d\'e2y b\'ecnh an m\'e0u \u273 o\u777  l\'ean tay c\u7853 u, tr\u7847 m gi\u7885 ng d\u7863 n d\'f2: "C\'e1ch nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia xa m\u7897 t ch\'fat, b\u7885 n ch\'fang mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t con, chi\u7871 m l\u7845 y con."\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n t\u7881 nh t\u7881 nh m\'ea m\'ea, sau khi v\u7873  nh\'e0 m\u7897 t th\'e1ng, m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\u7885  l\'fac v\u7915 a c\u417 m n\u432 \u7899 c xong, d\'e2y b\'ecnh an th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i t\u7921  nhi\'ean \u273 \u7913 t th\'e0nh hai \u273 o\u7841 n, ch\u7895  \u273 \u7913 t b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 t tr\u7909 i th\'e0nh m\'e0u \u273 en, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  ai \u273 \'f3 d\'f9ng thu\u7889 c l\'e1 \u273 \u7889 t l\'eca.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 ngo\uc0\u7841 i kinh h\'e3i, l\u7841 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng mang c\u7853 u \u273 i th\u259 m h\u7887 i v\u7883  \u273 \u7841 o nh\'e2n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 \u7841 o nh\'e2n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p b\u7885 n h\u7885 , ch\u7881  b\u7843 o \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7879  chuy\u7875 n l\u7901 i, n\'f3i Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7901 i sinh th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u7921 c h\u432  
\f2\i (h\uc0\u432  nh\u432 \u7907 c)
\f1\i0 , b\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7841 o h\u7841 nh ch\u432 a \u273 \u7911 , kh\'f4ng b\u7843 o v\u7879  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u, k\'eau b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i th\u7881 nh cao minh kh\'e1c. B\u7845 t lu\u7853 n van xin nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \u7841 o nh\'e2n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u g\u7863 p l\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'e1c ch\u7881  g\u7885 i b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i v\'e0o n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 ngo\uc0\u7841 i sau khi \u273 i ra v\'e0nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7887  \u7917 ng, t\u7921 a h\u7891  \u273 \'e3 kh\'f3c, b\'e0 d\u7851 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7901 i \u273 i, l\u7841 i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i c\u7847 u nh\u7919 ng "Cao nh\'e2n" kh\'e1c, nh\u432 ng v\u7883  \u273 \u7841 o nh\'e2n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c b\u7843 n l\u297 nh cao b\u7889 i ph\u7853 n l\u7899 n, c\'e1c \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n nghe nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7841 o nh\'e2n \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7873 u n\'f3i m\'ecnh \u273 \u7841 o h\u7841 nh ch\u432 a \u273 \u7911 , c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m th\u7917 , r\u7889 i r\'edt t\u7915  ch\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 o\u7841 n th\u7901 i gian kia n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i m\u7897 t t\u7845 c kh\'f4ng r\u7901 i tr\'f4ng coi c\u7853 u, c\'f3 l\u7869  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m m\u7845 t m\u7841 ng. M\'e0 b\u7903 i s\u7921  c\u7889  ng\'e3 \u7903  c\u7917 a h\'e0ng b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u7853 u v\u7915 a v\u7863 n ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i \u7903  nh\'e0, c\'f3 l\'e3o nh\'e2n ch\u7863 t ch\u7869  tr\'f4ng coi m\u7899 i tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u nguy hi\u7875 m. M\'e3i cho \u273 \u7871 n sau n\'e0y kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec \u273 \'f3, c\u7847 u c\u7913 u nh\'e0 m\u7865  \u273 \u7867  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, hao h\u7871 t t\'e2m t\u432  l\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t m\u7863 t d\'e2y chuy\u7873 n ng\u7885 c nghe n\'f3i l\'e0 linh ng\u7885 c t\u7893  truy\u7873 n, d\'f9ng d\'e2y b\'ecnh an x\'e2u l\u7841 i cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 eo b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, t\'ecnh h\'ecnh m\u7899 i kh\'e1 h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\'ecnh m\'f2 nh\u432  h\'ecnh v\u7899 i b\'f3ng kh\'f4ng g\u7841 t \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kia, th\u7853 m ch\'ed d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\'fang ph\'e1t ra nh\u7919 ng \'e2m ti\u7871 t v\'f4 ngh\u297 a ng\u7853 p tr\'e0n \'e1c \'fd, nh\u432 ng trong v\'f4 h\'ecnh t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7845 m m\'e0n ng\u259 n c\'e1ch c\u7853 u v\u7899 i ch\'fang, khi\u7871 n cho nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o d\u7877  d\'e0ng ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean, t\u7841 o th\'e0nh t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng th\u7921 c s\u7921  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y t\'e1c d\u7909 ng b\u7843 o v\u7879  c\u7911 a ng\u7885 c d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang suy y\u7871 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia c\'e1ch c\u7853 u c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ki\'eang n\u7875  g\'ec c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u259 m c\u7853 u ch\'edn tu\u7893 i, cha m\u7865  g\u7863 p tai n\u7841 n giao th\'f4ng, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i nu\'f4i d\u432 \u7905 ng, \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c n\u259 m hai \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i qua \u273 \u7901 i, m\'f9a thu n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i c\u361 ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i c\u7853 u, th\'e2n nh\'e2n trong nh\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fa, ch\'fa lu\'f4n b\u7873  b\u7897 n nhi\u7873 u c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c trong c\'f4ng ty, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 th\'e2n c\u7853 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i n\'f3i th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u7853 u h\u432  nh\u432 \u7907 c d\u7877  khi\u7871 n qu\u7927  qu\'e1i ghi nh\u7899 , kh\u7855 p n\u417 i nh\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7887 i th\u259 m, d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i c\u7847 u th\u7847 n l\u7841 y Ph\u7853 t l\u7841 i c\'e0ng c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7841 t coi th\u432 \u7901 ng, tuy r\u7857 ng v\'ec e ng\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0 trong nh\'e0 n\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n ng\u259 n c\u7843 n, nh\u432 ng lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng \u7911 ng h\u7897 . V\'ec v\u7853 y hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  t\'ecm bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  d\u7921 a v\'e0o b\u7843 n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng may cha m\u7865  c\'f3 \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i nh\'e0 c\u7917 a g\u7917 i ti\u7873 n v\'e0o ng\'e2n h\'e0ng cho c\u7853 u, \u7903  c\'f4ng ty c\u7911 a ch\'fa c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 c\u7893  ph\u7847 n, gia c\u7843 nh cha m\u7865  ngo\u7841 i t\u7893  gi\'e0u c\'f3, b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i b\u7903 i th\u432 \u417 ng con g\'e1i l\u7841 i c\'e0ng \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t thi\'ean v\u7883  c\u7853 u, cho t\u7899 i gi\u7901  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n t\'e0i s\u7843 n cha m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i cho c\u7853 u, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n gi\'fap c\u7853 u \u273 \u7847 u t\u432 , sau khi b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i qua \u273 \u7901 i c\u361 ng \u273 em t\'e0i s\u7843 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\u432 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \'edt cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c v\'ec sinh k\u7871  m\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n lu\'f4n s\u7889 ng trong s\u7907  h\'e3i m\u417  h\u7891 , b\u7903 i lo l\u7855 ng s\u7869  \u273 \u7897 t t\u7917  ch\u7871 t ho\u7863 c b\u7883  gi\u7871 t ch\u7871 t, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i khao kh\'e1t c\'f4ng th\'e0nh danh to\u7841 i, sau khi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p ch\u7881  t\'f9y ti\u7879 n t\'ecm m\u7897 t c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n chuy\'ean ng\'e0nh c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, tu\u7847 n t\u7921  m\'e0 ti\u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i di \u273 \u7897 ng ra nh\'ecn, 3:59, r\u7845 t t\'e0 m\'f4n, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n c\u7853 u b\u7915 ng t\u7881 nh t\u7915  trong \'e1c m\u7897 ng, nh\'ecn th\u7901 i gian \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 3:59. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u t\u7915  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 n g\u7863 p t\'e0 \u273 \u7909 ng qu\u7927  \u273 \'e3 nhi\u7873 u, ch\'fat chi ti\u7871 t v\u7909 n v\u7863 t n\'e0y c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u273 \u7875  trong l\'f2ng, ch\u7881  c\u7847 u kh\'f4ng l\'e0m h\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\'e0 t\u7889 t r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u7853 u c\u361 ng h\u7871 t bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 , l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ra xem \u7913 ng d\u7909 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng d\'f9ng, th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean m\u7841 ng vui th\'ec c\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7853 n th\'ec m\u7855 ng tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n vui v\u7867 , th\u7845 y b\u7841 n b\'e8 k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n nh\'e0 c\u7917 a sinh ho\u7841 t t\'ecnh h\'ecnh g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'e2y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng \'edt nh\'e2n kh\'ed, huy\u234 \u769 t di\u803 ch d\u7847 n d\u7847 n l\u432 u th\'f4ng, tr\'e1i tim \u273 ang \u273 \u7853 p th\u7853 t nhanh c\u361 ng t\u7915  t\u7915  b\'ecnh \u7893 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a s\u7889 ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  k\'e9o d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u7871 n 7h, \'e1nh n\u7855 ng ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  chi\u7871 u v\'e0o, l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i r\u7901 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 em \u273 \'e8n gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f9ng \u273 \'e8n ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch \u273 \u7873 u t\u7855 t, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 i r\u7917 a m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 n nh\'e0 cha m\u7865  \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i cho c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u7903  trong th\'e0nh ph\u7889  n\'e0y, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng ph\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  thi\'ean \'e2m, l\u7845 y \'e1nh s\'e1ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'e1i m\u7841 ng n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i cho, ch\u7881  khi \u273 \u7913 ng d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i r\u7921 c r\u7905  \u7845 m \'e1p m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kho\'e1i \'fd nh\u7865  nh\'f5m, khi \u273 \'f3 nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i kia c\u361 ng \'edt \u273 i r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, b\u7903 i v\u7853 y \u273 \'e3 \u273 em c\u259 n nh\'e0 kia cho thu\'ea, b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'ec t\'e1ch ra thu\'ea m\u7897 t c\u259 n ph\'f2ng h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i \u7903  g\u7847 n \u273 \u417 n v\u7883 , tr\u432 \u7899 c khi thu\'ea c\'f2n \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i xem qua, ph\'f2ng ch\u7885 n l\'e0 ph\'f2ng c\'f3 phong th\u7911 y t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed d\u7891 i d\'e0o nh\u7845 t \'97\'97 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7921 c k\'ec coi tr\u7885 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7873 u y\'ean t\'e2m l\'e0 v\'ec c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m t\u7915  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 n, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t b\u7885 n b\u7883 p b\u7907 m giang h\u7891  r\u7845 t th\u7841 o, h\u7847 u nh\u432  v\u7915 a \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t n\'f3i v\'e0i l\u7901 i li\u7873 n c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh hay ch\u7881  l\'e0 l\u7915 a b\u7883 p gi\u7843  danh d\'f9ng chi\'eau b\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \u7863 c th\'f9 b\u7843 n th\'e2n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i b\'e0i x\'edch gi\u7871 ng, g\u432 \u417 ng soi, \u273 \u7847 m n\u432 \u7899 c, c\'e1c lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7891  v\u7853 t hay n\u417 i c\'f3 \'e2m kh\'ed n\u7863 ng ho\u7863 c c\'f3 ch\'fat linh d\u7883 , m\u7863 c d\'f9 bi\u7871 t nh\u7921 a plastic kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t cho s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e, l\'fac \u259 n c\u417 m c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ki\'ean tr\'ec d\'f9ng b\'e1t \u273 \u361 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7871  t\u7841 o t\u7915  nh\u7921 a\'97\'97 \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n v\'ec c\'e0ng l\'e0 v\u7853 t ph\u7849 m c\'f4ng nghi\u7879 p kh\'f4ng c\'f3 linh t\'ednh, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng d\u7877  b\'e1m v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng trong nh\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  m\u7897 t t\u7845 m g\u432 \u417 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\u7847 n soi g\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7875  s\u7917 a sang l\u7841 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n, tr\'e1nh l\'fac \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i b\u7897  d\'e1ng qu\'e1 nh\u7871 ch nh\'e1c, v\'ec v\u7853 y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t m\u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7881  \u273 i\u7875 m n\u417 i th\'edch h\u7907 p nh\u7845 t trong nh\'e0 \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t t\u7845 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u r\u7917 a m\u7863 t xong \u273 i ra, nh\'ecn v\'e0o g\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7881 nh l\u7841 i t\'f3c, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y "Tr\'ec Di\'ean" trong g\u432 \u417 ng ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, nh\u7871 ch m\'f4i, n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng n\'e9m l\u432 \u7907 c x\'e1ch c\u7863 p c\'f4ng v\u259 n \u273 \u7841 p c\u7917 a lao ra ngo\'e0i, ng\u7891 i v\'e0o trong thang m\'e1y l\'f2ng v\u7851 n s\u7907  h\'e3i nh\u432  c\u361 .\cb1 \
\cb3 May m\uc0\u7855 n hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i l\'e0 gi\u7901  cao \u273 i\u7875 m bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng, ti\u7875 u khu n\'e0y g\u7847 n CBD, l\'e0 khu v\u7921 c s\u7847 m u\u7845 t, giao th\'f4ng thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n, ti\u7873 n thu\'ea kh\'f4ng r\u7867 , c\'e1c h\u7897  gia \u273 \'ecnh ch\u7911  y\u7871 u l\'e0 nh\'e2n vi\'ean v\u259 n ph\'f2ng, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y gi\u7901  n\'e0y thang m\'e1y \u273 \u7873 u chen l\u7845 n k\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\'f2n tho\'e1ng c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7917 i th\u7845 y h\u432 \u417 ng th\u417 m b\u7919 a s\'e1ng, h\u417 i th\u7903  cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a c\u7913 u v\u7899 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915  trong s\'e1t na kinh h\'e3i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i kia.\cb1 \

