\
\cb3 Hi\uc0\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 \u273 i\u7875 m t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t, \'e1p l\u7921 c kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u, c\'f3 vi\u7879 c xin ngh\u7881  t\u7841 m th\u7901 i c\u361 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i d\u7877  d\'e0ng, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\u432 \u417 ng th\u432 \u7903 ng s\u7869  k\'e9m \u273 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ti\u7873 m n\u259 ng ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n c\u361 ng b\u7883  gi\u7899 i h\u7841 n. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\'ecm vi\u7879 c l\'e0m \'e1p l\u7921 c l\u7899 n hay c\u226 \u768 n t\u259 ng ca, b\u7903 i c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t n\u7871 u m\'ecnh ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911  tinh th\u7847 n kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia s\u7869  c\'e0ng d\u7877  qu\u7845 n l\'ean, c\'f3 th\u7875  an an \u7893 n \u7893 n tr\'f4i qua th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng t\u7879  r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\'e1i xe h\u432 \u7899 ng th\u7859 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda n\'fai T\'e2y Thanh ngo\'e0i th\'e0nh, tr\'ean n\'fai T\'e2y Thanh c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n, trong t\u7881 nh c\u361 ng c\'f3 ch\'fat ti\u7871 ng t\u259 m, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng h\u432 \u417 ng h\u7887 a c\u361 ng v\u432 \u7907 ng. Trong qu\'e1n c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\u7883  \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng h\u7885  Tr\u432 \u417 ng, r\u7845 t c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7885 n nh\'e0 \u7903  v\'e0 b\'e0i tr\'ed nh\'e0 \u273 \u7873 u tr\u432 ng c\u7847 u \'fd ki\u7871 n c\u7911 a \'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7917 a \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \'e2m xu\u7889 ng, ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 t\u7915  ph\u432 \u417 ng xa truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng s\u7845 m r\u7873 n, trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7849 n \u7849 n c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7845 t an, \u273 \u7841 p ch\'e2n ga. T\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7899 i nay c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\'edch th\u7901 i ti\u7871 t m\u432 a d\u7847 m kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'e1nh m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i, lo\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t hung h\u259 ng ngang ng\u432 \u7907 c, h\u417 n n\u7919 a v\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i \'f4 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  v\u7889 n r\u7845 t th\u432 a th\u7899 t, nh\'e2n kh\'ed \u273 \u417 n b\u7841 c, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u c\'e0ng th\'eam b\u7845 t l\u7907 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 May m\'e0 l\'fac n\'e0y l\'e0 s\'e1ng s\uc0\u7899 m, v\u7841 n v\u7853 t \u273 \u7893 i m\u7899 i, s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng tr\'e0n tr\u7873 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7845 y ven \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 a tay v\u7851 y xe c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, t\u259 ng t\u7889 c lao \u273 i. Ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\u7899 i g\u7847 n, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 do s\'e1ng s\u7899 m hay do c\u7853 u suy ngh\u297  nhi\u7873 u, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i qua \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng mu\u7889 n \u273 i nh\u7901  xe\'97\'97 m\u7863 c d\'f9 \u7903  gi\u7919 a \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng tr\'ean qu\u7889 c l\u7897  n\'e0y, kh\u7843  n\u259 ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7867  loi tr\u417  tr\u7885 i \u273 i nh\u7901  c\u7921 c k\u7923  nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\'e2n v\u7853 t th\u432 \u7901 ng g\u7863 p trong phim linh d\u7883 , b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y g\'ec qu\'e1i l\u7841 , nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7871 n th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t t\u7915  nhi\u7873 u m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u th\u7845 y, c\u7853 u t\u7921  nhi\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi \uc0\u273 i v\'e0o trong ph\u7841 m vi \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nh\u7865  nh\'f5m t\u7915  trong ra ngo\'e0i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i do t\'e1c d\u7909 ng t\'e2m l\'fd hay kh\'f4ng, \u7903  lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0y c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\'ecnh m\'f2 v\'e0 \'e1c \'fd \u273 \u7873 u tho\'e1ng gi\u7843 m b\u7899 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec \uc0\u273 ang trong th\u7901 i gian l\'e0m vi\u7879 c, trong qu\'e1n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m quen thu\u7897 c n\u417 i n\'e0y \u273 i v\'e0o trong n\u7897 i vi\u7879 n, g\'f5 l\'ean c\'e1nh c\u7917 a g\u7895  th\u7913  hai b\'ean tr\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong c\uc0\u7917 a l\'e0 m\u7897 t thi\u7871 u ni\'ean \u273 \u7841 o \u273 \u7891 ng m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m m\u432 \u7901 i s\'e1u tu\u7893 i, c\u7853 u b\'e9 l\'e0 b\'e0 con xa v\u7899 i Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng, c\u361 ng l\'e0 \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7879  c\u7911 a \'f4ng, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c \u7903  trong n\u7897 i th\'e0nh, Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t v\u7899 i ngh\u7881  \u273 \'f4ng v\'e0 ngh\u7881  h\'e8 th\'ec tr\u7903  v\u7873  qu\'e1n h\u7895  tr\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7841 o \u273 \u7891 ng \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n ra Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng k\u7923  qu\'e1i, t\u7921  nhi\'ean n\'f3i: "Em \u273 i b\'e1o cho s\u432  ph\u7909 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o nh\'e2n nh\'ecn qua h\u417 n b\u7889 n m\u432 \u417 i tu\u7893 i, c\'f3 ch\'fat ph\'fac h\u7853 u, so v\u7899 i h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7871  ngo\u7841 i cao nh\'e2n \u273 \u7841 o c\u7889 t ti\'ean phong trong t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a \u273 \u7841 i ch\'fang v\u7851 n c\'f3 ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch kh\'f4ng nh\u7887 , nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\u7871 t \'f4ng l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh. L\'fac m\u7899 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  T\'f4 D\'e2n l\'e0m vi\u7879 c c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \u7903  c\u259 n h\u7897  hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i, v\'ec ng\'f4i nh\'e0 cha m\u7865  \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\'f3 kh\'e1ch thu\'ea n\'ean c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng chuy\u7875 n v\u7873  m\'e0 thu\'ea m\u7897 t c\u259 n h\u7897  nh\u7887  g\u7847 n \u273 \u417 n v\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 n h\u7897  nh\u7887  kia nh\'ecn th\'f4ng tho\'e1ng s\'e1ng s\u7911 a, k\'ec th\u7921 c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\u432  v\u7867  ngo\'e0i s\u7841 ch s\u7869 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  \u273 \'f3 hai tu\u7847 n li\u7873 n b\u7883  m\u7897 t th\u7913  qu\u7845 n l\'ean \'97 tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia \u7903  b\u7889 n ph\'eda xung quanh r\'ecnh m\'f2 m\'ecnh, c\u361 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean l\'e2m v\'e0o th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7845 t l\u7921 c g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng qu\u7927  d\u7883  nh\u432  s\'e1ng nay, nh\u432 ng t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh b\u7883  "Th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3" \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t qu\u7845 n l\'ean nh\u432  phim kinh d\u7883  l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nhi\u234 \u768 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean hoang mang lo s\u7907  \u273 i kh\u7855 p n\u417 i t\'ecm c\'e1ch c\u7913 u m\'ecnh, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\'e0 v\u7883  Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'e0y gi\'fap c\u7853 u gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t th\u7913  kia, c\'f2n thay c\u7853 u ch\u7885 n ch\u7895  \u7903  m\u7899 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u361 ng trong kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian \u273 \'f3 linh ng\u7885 c \u273 \'e3 ba l\u7847 n li\'ean ti\u7871 p thay c\u7853 u ng\u259 n c\u7843 n \u273 \u7841 i ki\u7871 p n\u7841 n sinh t\u7917 , sau \u273 \'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  ph\'f2ng h\u7897  d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng mong manh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i r\'f5 m\uc0\u7909 c \u273 \'edch \u273 \u7871 n v\u7899 i Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng, l\u7841 i thu\u7853 t l\u7841 i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh m\u7845 y ng\'e0y g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, bao g\u7891 m c\u7843  chuy\u7879 n s\'e1ng nay g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i, l\'f2ng \u273 \u7847 y ch\u7901  mong, h\u7887 i th\u259 m \'f4ng li\u7879 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 v\u7853 t hay ph\u432 \u417 ng ph\'e1p n\'e0o kh\'e1c thay th\u7871  linh ng\u7885 c b\u7843 o h\u7897  c\u7853 u hay kh\'f4ng. Nh\u432 ng trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t kh\u7843  n\u259 ng n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  qu\'e1 nh\u7887 , m\u7863 c d\'f9 \u273 \'e3 qua r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m, c\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\u7899  mang m\'e1ng n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i nh\u7901  c\u7853 y bao nhi\'eau ng\u432 \u7901 i hao t\u7893 n bao nhi\'eau t\'e2m l\u7921 c m\u7899 i th\u259 m d\'f2 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin t\u7913 c v\u7873  m\u7843 nh ng\u7885 c n\'e0y, c\u361 ng l\'e0 c\u417  duy\'ean x\u7843 o h\u7907 p nh\'e0 m\u7865  \u273 \u7867  c\u7911 a b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i l\u7841 i l\u432 u truy\u7873 n m\u7897 t m\u7843 nh linh ng\u7885 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y, b\'e0 m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7899 t lo l\u7855 ng chuy\u7879 n b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  l\'e0 bi\u7871 t ng\u7885 c c\'f9ng lo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng t\u7847 m th\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7853 t ngang c\u7845 p v\u7899 i n\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7843 o v\u7879  c\u7853 u b\'ecnh an kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng l\u7845 y t\u7899 i tay. Ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7845 t gi\u7919  lo\u7841 i v\u7853 t n\'e0y ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n thi\u7871 u m\u7841 ng kh\'f4ng thi\u7871 u ti\u7873 n, c\u7853 u c\'f3 hao h\u7871 t gia t\'e0i c\u361 ng ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t m\u7843 nh n\u7919 a. H\'f4m nay Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\u7871 u c\'f3 th\u7875  cung c\u7845 p cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t \'edt manh m\u7889 i, c\'f2n ch\u7881  cho c\u7853 u bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p t\u7841 m th\u7901 i b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 t\u7889 t l\u7855 m r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng, tr\u7847 m ng\'e2m m\u7897 t l\'e1t ch\u7853 m r\'e3i n\'f3i: "C\u361 ng th\u7853 t tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p, n\u7871 u con \u273 \u7871 n hai ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\'f3 l\u7869  ta c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c minh l\u7897  cho con, nh\u432 ng h\'f4m nay con \u273 \u7871 n, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i ta \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p ch\'ednh x\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra, qu\'e9t hai c\'e1i, \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i: "Ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y con bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean \uc0\u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i l\'e0 \u7843 nh m\u7897 t ch\'e0ng trai tr\u7867 , m\u7863 c s\u417  mi tr\u7855 ng qu\u7847 n d\'e0i \u273 en v\u7915 a gi\'e0 d\u7863 n l\u7841 i v\u7915 a s\u7841 ch s\u7869 , tr\'ean tay \u273 eo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891  ki\u7875 u c\u7893  b\u7857 ng da, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t tu\u7845 n m\u7929  s\u7855 c b\'e9n, \'e1nh m\u7855 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'e0n \u7843 nh r\u7891 i l\u7841 i \'f4n nh\'e3 khi\'eam t\u7889 n. Ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y v\'f4 lu\u7853 n b\u7873  ngo\'e0i hay kh\'ed ch\u7845 t \u273 \u7873 u l\u7897  ra v\u7867  xu\u7845 t ch\'fang, r\u7845 t d\u7877  khi\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ta l\u432 u l\u7841 i \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 ch\'fat quen thu\u7897 c, suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\'f3i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p gia \u7903  L\'e2m th\u7883  Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  r\u7845 t c\'f3 quy\u7873 n th\u7871 , \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng r\u7845 t n\u7893 i danh. Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  l\'e0 trung t\'e2m kinh t\u7871  ph\'eda \u273 \'f4ng, so v\u7899 i T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883  ph\u7891 n vinh h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u, ch\'fa c\u7911 a c\u7853 u sau n\'e0y c\u361 ng d\u7847 n d\u7901 i tr\u7909  s\u7903  c\'f4ng ty m\'ecnh \u273 \u7871 n Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883 , sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c c\u361 ng \u273 \'f3n \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i c\u7853 u t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3. Ngh\u7881  \u273 \'f4ng hay h\'e8 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  b\u7891 i \'f4ng b\'e0, cho n\'ean \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i khu\'f4n m\u7863 t n\'e0y c\'f3 ch\'fat \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (L\'e2m th\uc0\u7883 ,Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883 : th\u7883  \u7903  \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 th\'e0nh ph\u7889 )
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 i\u7875 m m\'e0n h\'ecnh \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\u7897 t c\'e1i, tho\'e1t \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p, l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 a \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho c\u7853 u. Ch\u7881  th\u7845 y ph\'eda tr\'ean l\'e0 m\u7897 t b\'e0i b\'e1o, ti\'eau \u273 \u7873  vi\u7871 t "7h s\'e1ng h\'f4m nay, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7853 p \u273 o\'e0n Di\u7879 p th\u7883  \u273 \'e3 qua \u273 \u7901 i v\'ec b\u7879 nh t\u7853 t".\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  mang m\'e1ng c\'f4ng ty c\u7911 a ch\'fa c\u7853 u h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\u361 ng c\'f3 l\'e0m \u259 n qua l\u7841 i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p gia, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean m\u7845 t l\'fac n\'e0o nghe ai n\'f3i g\'ec v\u7873  v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'e0y, Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  v\'e0 nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u quen bi\u7871 t g\u7885 i h\u7855 n m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng "Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 ", nghe v\'e0o tai gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7913 ng h\'e0ng l\'e3o tam, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7921 c s\u7921  n\u7855 m Di\u7879 p gia trong tay. Nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng nghe n\'f3i h\u7855 n t\u7915  nh\u7887  th\'e2n th\u7875  kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, ai lui t\u7899 i \u273 \u7873 u ch\'fa \'fd kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u h\u7855 n, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\'e0m h\u7855 n t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean qua \u273 \u7901 i v\'ec b\u7879 nh t\u7853 t, tuy l\'e0 ch\u7871 t tr\u7867 , nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u n\'e0o. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\u7853 u hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p g\u7863 p Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\'e0ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng quen bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n nh\'ecn t\u7845 m h\'ecnh k\'e8m theo trong b\'e0i b\'e1o kia, qu\u7843  nhi\'ean cho d\'f9 l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0n \u7843 nh, v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n s\u7855 c m\u7863 t h\u7855 n h\u417 i t\'e1i nh\u7907 t. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'ecnh nh\u432  r\u7845 t \'edt ch\u7909 p \u7843 nh, trong t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c b\'e0i b\'e1o \u273 \u432 a tin n\'f3i v\u7873  h\u7855 n, r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7845 m n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng nh\'ecn s\u7855 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, h\u7887 i: "Con bi\u7871 t?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u7841 ... Con bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t con."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng: "\u272 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng v\'ec sao l\u7841 i cho con xem c\'e1i n\'e0y \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'f3i: "S\'e1ng h\'f4m nay ta c\u7843 m \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c con s\u7869  \u273 \u7871 n, l\'fac xem tin t\u7913 c v\u7915 a hay nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p v\u7883  Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh n\'e0y, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n h\u7855 n gi\u7889 ng t\u432 \u7899 ng \'e1c qu\u7927  trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t. L\'fac m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u ta v\u7851 n ch\u432 a d\'e1m ch\u7855 c, d\'f9 sao t\u432 \u7899 ng \'e1c qu\u7927  ngh\'ecn n\u259 m kh\'f3 g\u7863 p, sau \u273 \'f3 tra x\'e9t th\'e2n th\u7871  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, k\u7871 t h\u7907 p ng\'e0y sinh ng\'e0y gi\u7895 , l\u7841 i th\'eam cu\u7897 c \u273 \u7901 i h\u7855 n b\u7845 t ph\'e0m nh\u432 ng tr\'e1ng ni\'ean m\u7845 t s\u7899 m, l\'fac \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi ho\uc0\u7863 c n\'f3i: "T\u432 \u7899 ng \'e1c qu\u7927  l\'e0 g\'ec \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'f3i: "Ta c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p qua, ch\u7881  t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y trong ghi ch\'e9p, ghi ch\'e9p n\'f3i to\'e0n th\'e2n ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7899 ng \'e1c qu\u7927  d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c kh\'ed t\u7913 c t\'e0 s\'e1t, qu\u7927  th\u7847 n tr\'e1nh lui, m\u7879 nh c\'e1ch *\u273 \u7841 i khai \u273 \u7841 i h\u7907 p kh\'f4ng ch\u7895  ki\'eang k\u7883 , nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i l\'e0 m\u7879 nh qu\u7927  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\u7879 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i, th\u432 \u7901 ng hay ch\u7871 t s\u7899 m."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (\uc0\u273 \u7841 i tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 i h\u7907 p: hi\u7875 u n\'f4m na l\'e0 co \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\'e3n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng b\u7883  h\'ecnh kh\u7855 c hay ki\'eang k\u7883  g\'ec)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean qua l\u7841 i nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n, c\u361 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i quen thu\u7897 c c\u7853 u, n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1 t\'f9y \'fd, l\'fac n\'e0y l\u7841 i tr\u7847 m ng\'e2m m\u7897 t l\'e1t m\u7899 i n\'f3i: "Ta v\u7915 a th\u7845 y v\u7883  Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh n\'e0y li\u7873 n ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n t\'ednh m\u7841 ng con ch\u432 a t\u7899 i tuy\u7879 t l\u7897 , n\'ean con s\u7869  \u273 u\u7893 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y xin ta c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng con. Nh\u432 ng bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i do ta t\'ecnh c\u7901  bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  v\u259 n t\u7921  kh\u7855 c tr\'ean bia \u273 \'e1 l\u432 u truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901 , kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u272 \u7841 o m\'f4n ch\'ednh th\u7889 ng, ta c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i cho con, nh\u432 ng con kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c l\'e0 ta n\'f3i cho con bi\u7871 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n n\'e0y r\u7845 t \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n qu\u7927  th\u7847 n qu\'e1i d\u7883  n\'e0y, d\'f9 c\u7853 u c\'f3 ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 i n\'f3i ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tin. Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3ng l\'f2ng gi\u7919  m\u7841 ng, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c cam \u273 oan: "V\'e2ng, con tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng n\'f3i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng nh\u7865  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, n\'f3i: "Con ngh\u297  c\'e1ch l\u7845 y tro c\u7889 t c\u7911 a v\u7883  Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh n\'e0y, mang theo t\'f9y th\'e2n tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7841 i ng\'e0y ng\'e0y th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng b\'e0i v\u7883  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n trong nh\'e0, nh\u432  v\u7853 y s\u7869  c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7845 n \'e1p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kia kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\u7899 i g\u7847 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Bi\uc0\u7879 n ph\'e1p l\u7845 y tro ng\u432 \u7901 i mang theo t\'f9y th\'e2n b\'ean m\'ecnh n\'e0y nghe v\'e0o tai c\'f3 ch\'fat qu\u7927  d\u7883 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u417 i do d\u7921 : "Vi\u7879 c n\'e0y..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, quay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7845 y hai t\u7845 m ph\'f9 b\'ecnh an \u273 \u432 a cho c\u7853 u: "Bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p n\'e0y c\'f3 d\'f9ng hay kh\'f4ng to\'e0n b\u7897  do con, con mu\u7889 n th\u7917  th\'ec c\u7913  th\u7917  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e2m r\u7891 i, t\u7915  khi bi\u7871 t th\u7871  gi\u7899 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, c\'f9ng v\u7899 i linh kh\'ed linh ng\u7885 c \u273 ang hao m\'f2n, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t t\u432 \u417 ng lai s\u7869  ch\u7881  c\'e0ng th\'eam nguy hi\u7875 m. D\'f9 sao t\'ecnh h\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 nh\u432  v\u7853 y, kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng c\'f2n n\u432 \u7899 c c\'f2n t\'e1t, t\u7841 m th\u7901 i th\u7917  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n xem sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n h\u7887 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "Chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh kia kh\'f4ng g\'e2y \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng ch\u7913  \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7855 c l\u7855 c tay, t\'f9y \'fd n\'f3i: "C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\'f4 h\u7891 n o\'e1n qu\u7927 , ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7871 t l\'e0 ch\u7871 t, c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng g\'ec."\cb1 \
