\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng ch\u7881  \u273 i\u7875 m, trong l\'f2ng h\u417 i b\'ecnh t\u297 nh xu\u7889 ng, n\u7871 u n\'f3i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t v\u7889 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t m\'e0n s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \'edt nh\u7845 t t\u7915  trong s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7909 c ti\'eau, tuy r\u7857 ng l\u7845 y tro c\u7889 t c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac c\uc0\u7853 u l\'e1i xe v\u7873  \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u, v\'ec tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7847 y m\'e2y n\'ean trong nh\'e0 c\'f3 ch\'fat \'e1m t\u7889 i. \u272 \'eam qua v\'ec g\u7863 p \'e1c m\u7897 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u, l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u417 n bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  ng\u259 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\'e9o t\u7899 i, qua loa thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o li\u7873 n n\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7855 m nghi\u7873 n hai m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'fac nh\uc0\u432  t\u7881 nh nh\u432  m\u417 , c\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng lo\u7865 t xo\u7865 t nh\u432  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i mang d\'e9p l\'ea kh\u7869  \u273 i qua \u273 i l\u7841 i, c\u7853 u c\u7889  m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra nh\'ecn, c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong ph\'f2ng qu\'e1 t\u7889 i, mu\u7889 n m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n, \'fd th\u7913 c thanh t\u7881 nh, th\'e2n th\u7875  th\u7871  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7897 ng n\u7893 i m\u7897 t ng\'f3n tay \'97\'97 lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng tr\u7843 i qua, c\u361 ng c\'f3 b\'e1o khoa h\u7885 c gi\u7843 i th\'edch nguy\'ean nh\'e2n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u tr\'ean th\'e2n ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7917  d\u7909 ng khoa h\u7885 c \u273 \u7875  gi\u7843 i th\'edch, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u th\'ec ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 em l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd to\'e0n th\'e2n t\u7853 p trung \u7903  m\u7843 nh ng\u7885 c tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 ch\'fat th\u7903  kh\'f4ng ra h\u417 i, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean, ti\u7871 ng \u273 i l\u7841 i tr\'ean s\'e0n bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u361 ng m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c \'fd th\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'ean g\u7889 i vang l\'ean, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 vang bao l\'e2u, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng c\u7847 m l\u7845 y, m\'e0n h\'ecnh hi\u7879 n l\'ean "Ch\'fa" .\cb1 \
\cb3 "D\uc0\u7841  ch\'fa, c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec sao \u7841 ?" L\'fac n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n m\u7899 i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7893  h\u7885 ng kh\'f4 kh\u7889 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t b\'ean n\'f3i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, m\u7897 t b\'ean xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7847 m c\u7889 c \u273 i v\'e0o b\u7871 p r\'f3t n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa c\uc0\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh h\'e0n huy\'ean v\u7899 i c\u7853 u v\'e0i c\'e2u, h\u7887 i han t\'ecnh h\'ecnh g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y, r\u7845 t nhanh v\'e0o th\u7859 ng v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 : " Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t ng\'e0y kia con tr\u7903  v\u7873  m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n \u273 i? Tang l\u7877  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , b\'e2y gi\u7901  ch\'fa \u273 ang \u7903  n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i b\u7853 n c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c kh\'f4ng th\u7875  v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, con v\u7899 i m\u7907  \u273 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n. C\u361 ng nh\'e2n c\u417  h\u7897 i quen bi\u7871 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u417 n, bi\u7871 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7899 i ch\'fa kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 r\u7845 t g\u7847 n g\u361 i, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 hi\u7873 m kh\'edch g\'ec, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng hi\u7875 u r\'f5 \u7903  trong l\'f2ng ch\'fa b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\'ecnh h\u417 n ph\'e2n n\u7917 a l\'e0 m\u7851 u ng\u432 \u7901 i "Kh\'f4ng ra h\u7891 n", tu\u7893 i c\'f2n tr\u7867  v\'f9i \u7903  ch\u7913 c v\u7909  kh\'f4ng ti\u7873 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\'e0y n\'e0o hay ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng ch\'ed ti\u7871 n th\u7911 . Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7871  h\u7879  ch\'fa t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng l\'fac n\'e0o c\u361 ng lu\'f4n xoay quanh "Th\'eam b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u th\'eam \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i", c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7901 i tham gia tang l\u7877  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'edt nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 ch\'fat ph\'e2n l\u432 \u7907 ng, quen bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t hai b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u d\'f9 sao v\u7851 n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n t\u7889 t. \u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean nguy\'ean nh\'e2n ch\u7911  y\u7871 u l\'e0 c\'f4 em h\u7885  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 ang h\u7885 c \u7903  n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i, th\'e2n th\'edch b\'ean kia c\u7911 a m\u7907  ch\'fa c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  v\'e0o m\u7855 t, tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p n\'e0y chung quy c\u7913  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i c\'f9ng m\u7907  th\'ec s\u7869  t\u7889 t h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u l\'e0 th\u432 \u7901 ng ng\'e0y, d\'f9 c\'f3 l\'e0 tang l\u7877  l\'e3o t\u7917  Thi\'ean V\u432 \u417 ng th\'ec Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng s\u7869  l\u7849 n \u273 i th\u7853 t xa, c\'f2n s\u7907  tr\'e1nh kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p, l\u7847 n n\'e0y l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'fang l\'fac ng\u7911  g\u7853 t c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i k\'ea g\u7889 i cho.\cb1 \
