\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297  c\u7843  hai ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch th\u7901 i gian c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0 bao, \'edt nh\u7845 t xe n\'e0y tuy l\'e2u h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat nh\u432 ng ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7903  v\u7873 , ch\u7901  ban qu\u7843 n l\'fd th\'ec kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i ch\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n bao gi\u7901 , b\'e8n l\'ean xe, ng\u7891 i \u7903  ch\u7895  tr\u7889 ng ph\'eda sau g\u7847 n c\u7917 a s\u7893 , b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng trung ni\'ean v\u7841 m v\u7905  m\u7863 c \'e1o jacket ng\u7891 i \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7845 y th\u7871  l\u7841 i d\u7883 ch d\u7883 ch v\'e0o trong. Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t s\u7869  d\u7877  b\u7883  say xe, h\'f4m nay b\'f4n ba m\u7897 t ng\'e0y, tinh th\u7847 n l\u7841 i kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng cao \u273 \u7897  li\'ean t\u7909 c, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u259 n c\u417 m \u273 \'e0ng ho\'e0ng, l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u7847 u \u273 au \'e2m \u7881 , li\u7873 n d\u7921 a \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o c\u7917 a s\u7893  xe nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i m\u7897 t l\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t n\'e0y li\u7873 n tr\u7903  n\'ean m\u417  h\u7891 . C\u7853 u li\'ean t\u7909 c l\'e2m v\'e0o tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i n\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea, v\u7851 n l\u7901  m\u7901  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c xe kh\'e1ch th\u7855 ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u7895  v\'e0o b\u7871 n, ti\u7871 ng h\'e0nh kh\'e1ch k\'e9o h\'e0nh l\'fd \u273 i \u273 i l\u7841 i l\u7841 i xu\u7889 ng xe, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n m\'ea man kh\'f4ng t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n khi c\u7853 u tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  thanh t\u7881 nh th\'ec s\u7855 c tr\u7901 i to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \'e3 t\u7889 i \u273 en, ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  m\'e0n \u273 \'eam \u273 en k\u7883 t, c\'f9ng v\u7899 i b\'f3ng n\'fai ph\'eda xa h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda con ng\u432 \u7901 i \'e1p t\u7899 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ra nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua, \u273 \'e3 m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  hai m\u432 \u417 i, ph\u7887 ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f2n c\'e1ch T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883  kh\'f4ng xa. Con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  n\'e0y v\u7899 i con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'fac \u273 i kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nhau, c\u7853 u v\u7853 y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng h\u7873  nh\u7853 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean xe ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i l\u7867  t\u7867  b\u7843 y t\'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 \u273 i T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883  gi\u7889 ng c\u7853 u. \u272 \u7841 i ca l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7891 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u ch\u7855 c kh\'f4ng th\'edch chen ch\'fac, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o \u273 \'e3 chuy\u7875 n l\'ean ng\u7891 i \u7903  gh\u7871  tr\u7889 ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c. C\u7853 u ng\u7891 i \u7903  h\'e0ng th\u7913  hai t\u7915  d\u432 \u7899 i l\'ean, ph\'eda sau ch\'ednh l\'e0 h\'e0ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng cao nh\u7845 t, h\'f4m nay tr\u7915  c\u7853 u ra, nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f2n l\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u ng\u7891 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, r\u7843 i r\'e1c \u7903  trong xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u432 \u7899 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i trong ch\u7889 c l\'e1t, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 , li\u7873 n t\u7855 t m\'e0n h\'ecnh chu\u7849 n b\u7883  c\u7845 t \u273 i. Trong l\'fac l\u417  \u273 \'e3ng, m\'e0n h\'ecnh \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\'e0u \u273 en nh\u7853 n \'e1nh s\'e1ng y\u7871 u \u7899 t t\u7915  \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7901  m\u7901  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 , ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u m\u7863 t m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i ph\'eda sau c\u7853 u\'97\'97 khu\'f4n m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch, ng\u361  quan c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901 , kh\'f4ng ch\'fat bi\u7875 u t\'ecnh, m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 ang tr\u7915 ng tr\u7915 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'f4ng t\u417  d\u7921 ng \u273 \u7913 ng. Gi\u7843  b\u7897  nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec l\u7841 i c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i l\'ean, tay kh\u7869  c\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng h\u417 i run r\u7849 y, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \'f4\u803 ng, c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean suy ngh\u297 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u432  duy trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'f3ng b\u259 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'ec ho\'e3n trong ch\uc0\u7889 c l\'e1t, gi\u7843  v\u7901  tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7863 ng l\u7869  t\u7915  trong t\'fai l\u7845 y ra ph\'f9 b\'ecnh an do Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng v\u7869  \'97 ph\'f9 b\'ecnh an t\u7893 ng c\u7897 ng c\'f3 hai t\u7845 m, m\u7897 t t\u7845 m c\u7853 u d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7921 ng tro c\u7889 t, m\u7897 t t\u7845 m kh\'e1c v\u7851 n lu\'f4n mang b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7875  trong t\'fai.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c trong l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh, m\'e9p t\u7845 m ph\'f9 m\'e0u v\'e0ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t t\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o \u273 \'e3 ch\'e1y \u273 en, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u gi\u7843  v\u7901  nh\u432  v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra th\u7913  \u273 \u7857 ng sau, l\u432 ng \u273 eo balo v\u7883 n th\'e0nh gh\u7871  chuy\u7875 n l\'ean ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng h\'e0ng gh\u7871  ph\'eda sau ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng trung ni\'ean l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7863 t balo xu\u7889 ng ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh, \'f4 t\'f4 \u273 \'e3 ti\u7871 n v\'e0o n\u7897 i th\'e0nh, c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  c\u361 ng d\u7847 n tr\u7903  n\'ean s\u7847 m u\u7845 t. Xung quanh c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean l\'e0m c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tho\'e1ng an t\'e2m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ra \'e2m th\u7847 m li\u7871 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn, ng\'f3n tay \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean m\'e0n h\'ecnh l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7913 ng l\u7841 i\'97\'97 c\'e1i "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" kia v\u7851 n ng\u7891 i \u7903  ph\'eda sau c\u7853 u, n\'f3 \u273 i theo c\u7853 u c\'f9ng chuy\u7875 n l\'ean ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7845 y kinh nghi\u7879 m c\'e1 nh\'e2n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\'e0 n\'f3i, ng\u432 \u7901 i gan d\u7841  s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7883  d\u7885 a \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i qu\'e1 s\u7907 , m\u7895 i l\u7847 n g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i th\u7913  n\'e0y, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t l\'e0 r\'f5 r\'e0ng n\'f3 ch\u7881  h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  m\'ecnh v\'e0 \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7907  h\'e3i, ho\u7843 ng lo\u7841 n, kinh s\u7907 , qua nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y vi\u7879 c duy nh\u7845 t h\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0 \'edt nh\u7845 t ph\u7843 i b\u7843 o tr\'ec v\u7867  ngo\'e0i tr\u7845 n t\u297 nh, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7883  s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c ch\'e2n tay lu\u7889 ng cu\u7889 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 m\u7845 t b\'ecnh t\u297 nh m\'e0 l\'e0m ra h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng g\'ec qu\'e1 kh\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u bi\u7871 t b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi theo nh\u432  l\u7901 i Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'f3i th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng hay kh\'f4ng, \'edt nh\u7845 t ng\u7885 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c b\u7843 o h\u7897  c\u7853 u m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian n\u7919 a, cho n\'ean c\u7889  gi\u7919  tr\u7845 n t\u297 nh ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi \'f4 t\'f4 v\'e0o b\u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng th\u7913  kia \u273 i theo c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4 D\'e2n th\uc0\u7883  k\'e9m h\u417 n Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  l\'e0 trong \u273 \'eam h\'e8, cho \u273 \u7871 n khi tr\u7901 i s\'e1ng Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n r\u7921 c r\u7905  ng\u7921 a xe nh\u432  n\u432 \u7899 c, l\'fac xu\u7889 ng xe \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 ban \u273 \'eam m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901 , con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a b\'e3i \u273 \u7895  xe b\u7871 n xe Kh\'ed V\u7853 n n\'e0y t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i l\u7879 ch, \u273 i ra \u273 \u7841 i l\u7897  c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i m\u7845 t b\u7843 y t\'e1m ph\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo s\'e1t ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng trung ni\'ean xu\u7889 ng xe tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, l\u7845 y d\u361 ng kh\'ed ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n n\'f3i: "\u272 \u7841 i ca nh\'e0 \u7903  \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 n c\u7913  theo kinh nghi\u7879 m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh ch\'ednh tr\u7921 c tr\'e1ng ni\'ean s\u7869  c\'f3 d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed d\u7891 i d\'e0o, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  c\'e1ch kh\'e1 xa. V\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  l\'fac h\u7885 c \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, ba ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 thanh ni\'ean tu\u7893 i thanh xu\'e2n, l\'fac \u7845 y \u7903  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  t\u7847 n su\u7845 t g\u7863 p t\'e0 ho\u7863 c b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u nh\u7887  h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i c\u7853 u hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  \u7903  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n d\uc0\u7883 ch sang b\'ean c\u7841 nh hai b\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i d\u7845 u v\u7871 t, tho\'e1ng c\'e1ch xa Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t ch\'fat, m\u7899 i h\u417 i ch\u7847 n ch\u7915  tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "Khu Thi\'ean Long."\cb1 \
\cb3 Khu Thi\'ean Long \uc0\u7903  ngay b\'ean c\u7841 nh ti\u7875 u khu Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7889 ng, c\u7853 u vui m\u7915 ng trong b\u7909 ng, c\'f9ng nam nh\'e2n ch\u7853 m r\'e3i tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n \u273 i t\u7899 i \u273 \u7841 i l\u7897 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7845 t s\u7907  b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\u7897 t th\'e2n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh v\u7851 y xe \u273 \'eam khuya, \u273 i tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\u7871 u g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 th\'ec c\u7913  gi\u7843  v\u7901  nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n r\u7891 i nhanh ch\'f3ng ch\u7841 y xa l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u v\u7851 y xe g\u7863 p tr\'fang l\'e1i xe kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec kh\'f4ng ch\u7841 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  th\u7871 . Ra \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7841 i l\u7897  c\u7853 u li\u7873 n th\u7915 a d\u7883 p \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i chung m\u7897 t xe tr\u7903  v\u7873 , nam nh\'e2n kia do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\u361 ng \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi xe taxi d\uc0\u7915 ng l\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n ng\u7891 i v\'e0o gh\u7871  l\'e1i ph\u7909 , nam nh\'e2n ng\u7891 i \u7903  gh\u7871  ph\'eda sau, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7889  \'fd nh\'ecn nh\'ecn, t\u7915  khi b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'ean xe, th\u7913  kia li\u7873 n d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 i theo n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u7883 a \u273 i\u7875 m, \u273 i ti\u7875 u khu Hoa Dung m\u7899 i, khu \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 CBD m\u7899 i m\u7903  r\u7897 ng, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c xem nh\u432  l\'e0 n\u417 i ph\u7891 n th\u7883 nh nh\u7845 t T\'f4 D\'e2n hi\u7879 n gi\u7901 , \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  v\'e0 nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (CBD: khu trung t\'e2m kinh t\uc0\u7871  th\u432 \u417 ng m\u7841 i d\u7883 ch v\u7909 )
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e1i xe l\'e0 m\uc0\u7897 t thanh ni\'ean tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i, nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i: "Anh \u273 \u7865 p trai th\u7855 t d\'e2y an to\'e0n v\'e0o, sao kh\'f4ng ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7857 ng sau, gh\u7871  ph\u7909  kh\'f4ng r\u7897 ng b\u7857 ng gh\u7871  sau \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn v\uc0\u7873  ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i ph\'eda sau, c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec, b\u7899 t chen ch\'fac."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e1i xe nh\'ecn c\uc0\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i, kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 ang suy ngh\u297  g\'ec, tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  khi l\'ean xe v\u7883  \u273 \u7841 i ca kia li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng quen bi\u7871 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, c\u361 ng im l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn khung c\u7843 nh th\'e0nh ph\u7889  quen thu\u7897 c b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n n\u417 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7845 y v\'ed da ra tr\u7843  ti\u7873 n, c\u7853 u nh\'ecn l\u7841 i, v\u7883  \u273 \u7841 i ca kia kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o \u273 \'e3 xu\u7889 ng xe \u273 \u7913 ng ch\u7901  \u7903  ngo\'e0i xe. Khu Thi\'ean Long c\'e1ch n\u417 i n\'e0y c\'f2n m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat \u273 i b\u7897 , nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0 t\'ednh xa, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y k\u7923  qu\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7875 u ca l\'e1i xe c\u7847 m l\u7845 y nh\'e2n d\'e2n t\u7879  nh\'ecn th\u7853 t k\u7929 , l\u7841 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, t\u7921 a h\u7891  mu\u7889 n n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\u7841 i ng\u7853 m mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean xu\uc0\u7889 ng xe, v\u7883  \u273 \u7841 i ca kia g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "C\u7843 m \u417 n c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean cho l\'e0 \uc0\u273 ang n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n ti\u7873 n xe, l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, xua tay m\u7897 t c\'e1i n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec." \u272 \'e1ng ra ph\u7843 i l\'e0 c\u7853 u c\'e1m \u417 n m\u7899 i \u273 \'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n trung ni\'ean n\'f3i n\'f3i: "Ti\uc0\u7875 u huynh \u273 \u7879 , v\u7853 y t\'f4i v\u7873  th\u259 m nh\'e0 m\u7897 t ch\'fat, t\u7915  bi\u7879 t t\u7915  \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng c\u432 \u7901 i t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, quay ng\u432 \u7901 i chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda ti\u7875 u khu c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7907 t nghe \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng l\u7849 m b\u7849 m m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "Tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\'f3 c\'e1i g\'ec \u273 \'f3, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u7903  qu\'e1 g\u7847 n c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n ch\u432 a thu h\u7891 i n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7913 ng m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901  nghi\'eam m\u7863 t quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn, \u273 \'fang l\'fac nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\'f3ng l\u432 ng nam nh\'e2n trung ni\'ean kia \u273 ang \u273 i xa, \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0u cam s\'e1ng r\u7921 c \u7903  c\u7893 ng ti\u7875 u khu chi\u7871 u xu\u7889 ng, r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y, n\'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\'f3ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean run l\uc0\u7849 y b\u7849 y, g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 m n\u7893 i ch\'eca kho\'e1, c\u7853 u nhanh ch\'f3ng ch\u7841 y v\'e0o trong t\'f2a nh\'e0, l\'fac c\u7917 a thang m\'e1y m\u7903  ra th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 i v\'e0o \'97\'97 c\u7853 u s\u7907  l\u7841 i g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n thu\u7903  nh\u7887  \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \'e3 phai nh\u7841 t, t\u7915  khi b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i \u273 em ng\u7885 c \u273 \u432 a cho c\u7853 u, tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i t\'e0, nh\u432 ng h\u7847 u nh\u432  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0o li\'ean ti\u7871 p "Nh\'ecn th\u7845 y" nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kh\'f4ng s\u7841 ch s\u7869  kia nh\u432  m\u7845 y ng\'e0y g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u s\u7901  m\u7843 nh ng\u7885 c tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, trong l\'fac l\u417  \u273 \'e3ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7921 ng tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, y\'ean l\u7863 ng t\u7921  an \u7911 i m\'ecnh m\u7863 c k\u7879  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\'e1i g\'ec, c\u7913  gi\u7843  v\u7901  kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \'edt nh\u7845 t ch\'fang n\'f3 v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p h\u7841 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7921  an \u7911 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\u361 ng su\'f4n s\u7867  \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7917 a nh\'e0, nghi th\u7847 n nghi qu\u7927  nh\'ecn xung quanh m\u7897 t ch\'fat, m\u7899 i m\u7903  c\u7917 a \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t kh\u7855 c b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n l\'ean \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i n\'e0y, c\u7853 u g\u7847 n nh\u432  to\'e0n th\'e2n m\u7845 t h\u7871 t s\u7913 c l\u7921 c co qu\u7855 p n\u7857 m tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng r\u7845 t nhanh Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i ki\'ean tr\'ec x\u7889 c l\u7841 i tinh th\u7847 n, t\'ecm b\'e0i v\u7883  v\u7899 i l\u432  h\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  t\u7889 t, nghi\'eam nghi\'eam c\u7849 n c\u7849 n \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean tr\'ean m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c b\'e0n nh\u7887  trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch. C\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng n\'e0y trong bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i l\u7897  ra v\'e0i ph\u7847 n qu\u7927  d\u7883 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 nam nh\'e2n \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n s\u7889 ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng trong nh\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\'e1ch, cho n\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7853 n t\'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7921 a theo l\u7901 i Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'f3i, c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i mang theo tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7875  b\u7843 o v\u7879  m\'ecnh, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  ng\'e0y mang theo \u7845 y m\u7895 i s\u7899 m t\u7889 i \u273 \u7873 u ph\u7843 i th\u7855 p h\u432 \u417 ng cho b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t l\u7847 n m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7853 m tr\u7877 , b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \'e3 mang tro c\u7889 t c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u7853 u li\u7873 n \u273 \u7889 t ba n\'e9n nhang cho b\'e0i v\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0i v\uc0\u7883  l\'e0m theo y\'eau c\u7847 u to\'e0n th\'e2n \u273 en huy\u7873 n, ph\'eda tr\'ean c\'f3 kh\u7855 c s\'e1u ch\u7919  m\'e0u v\'e0ng "Di\u7879 p th\u7883  Ngh\'eanh Chi chi linh" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7847 m nhang trong tay c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u cung k\'ednh b\'e1i l\u7841 y, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7855 m nhang v\'e0o l\u432  h\u432 \u417 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0i v\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau l\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u, m\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng th\u7859 ng, tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c nh\'ecn c\u7853 u l\'e0m t\u7845 t c\u7843 .\cb1 \
