\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t v\'ec t\'e2m l\'fd v\u7851 n c\'f2n qu\'e1 m\u7879 t m\u7887 i hay l\'e0 v\'ec tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  th\u7853 t s\u7921  che ch\u7903  c\u7853 u tr\u259 m t\'e0 tr\'e1nh lui, m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ng\u7911  \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t y\'ean \u7893 n, m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng m\u7897 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng m\u7885 i khi trong l\'fac n\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea lu\'f4n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3 r\'ecnh m\'f2 t\u7915  b\u7889 n ph\u432 \u417 ng t\'e1m h\u432 \u7899 ng m\'e0 li\'ean t\u7909 c ph\u7853 p ph\u7891 ng lo s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t gi\u7845 c n\'e0y \u273 em t\u7845 t c\u7843  thi\u7871 u ng\u7911  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c b\u7893  sung tr\u7903  v\u7873 , sau khi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901  tr\u432 a, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tinh th\u7847 n ph\u7845 n ch\u7845 n, \u273 i v\'e0o b\u7871 p n\u7845 u m\u7897 t n\u7891 i m\'ec g\'f3i, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean m\'fac m\u7897 t b\'e1t m\'ec nh\u7887  chan n\u432 \u7899 c m\'ec b\'e0y l\'ean tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. B\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7875  ch\u7845 t kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7897 ng v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n t\u7915 ng tr\u7843 i qua t\u7915  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7845 t tin nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y, n\u7871 u nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 c\u7847 u Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh che ch\u7903 , li\u7873 n th\'e0nh t\'e2m th\'e0nh \'fd m\'e0 l\'e0m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7863 t m\'ec xu\u7889 ng, xin l\u7895 i n\'f3i: "\u7910 y khu\u7845 t Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh, t\'f4i d\u7853 y mu\u7897 n h\u7841 i ng\'e0i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7919 a s\'e1ng, c\'f9ng t\'f4i \u259 n b\u7919 a tr\u432 a \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n nh\'e9."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\u7853 y sau \u273 \'f3 qua h\u417 n ba th\'e1ng, th\u7901 i ti\u7871 t d\u7847 n d\u7847 n chuy\u7875 n l\u7841 nh, m\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'fang l\'e0 v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\'ecnh an v\'f4 s\u7921 , ngay c\u7843  \'e1c m\u7897 ng c\u361 ng \'edt g\u7863 p, th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 \u273 \u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 b\'e1ch t\'e0 tr\'e1nh lui.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sinh ho\uc0\u7841 t r\u7845 t c\'f3 quy lu\u7853 t, t\'ednh c\'e1ch c\u361 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i tr\u7841 ch, c\'f4ng t\'e1c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n giao ti\u7871 p x\'e3 giao, sau khi tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian linh ng\u7885 c h\u7897  th\'e2n d\u7847 n m\u7845 t t\'e1c d\u7909 ng b\u7883  qu\u7927  qu\'e1i qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u lo s\u7907 , cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh tr\u7903  l\u7841 i. M\u7895 i ng\'e0y s\'e1ng s\u7899 m \u273 i l\'e0m, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i v\u7873  nh\'e0 n\u7845 u c\u417 m, c\u7853 u ng\'e0y c\'e0ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p c\u7911 a Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843 , m\'ecnh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi che ch\u7903 , ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e2n ng\'e0y Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t \u273 i quy\'ean g\'f3p cho \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n \u259 n g\'ec c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'ean d\'e2ng cho b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n, h\u7879 t nh\u432  trong nh\'e0 c\'f3 th\'eam m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i nhi\u7873 u th\'eam m\u7897 t mi\u7879 ng \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 th\uc0\u7913  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ch\'ednh l\'e0, m\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  sau l\u432 ng c\u7853 u, h\u417 n n\u7919 a h\'ecnh b\'f3ng c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng \u273 \u7853 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac c\uc0\u7853 u \u259 n c\u417 m, b\'f3ng \u273 en kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'f4\u803 ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7891  tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901 , ch\u7881  ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t b\'ean nh\'ecn c\u7853 u; l\'fac c\u7853 u t\u7855 m, b\'f3ng \u273 en c\u361 ng \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  sau m\'e0n n\u432 \u7899 c h\u417 i m\u7887 ng l\u7859 ng l\u7863 ng ch\u7901 ; Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'ec \u273 \u7875  l\'fac ng\u7911  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7887 a s\u7913 c l\u259 n l\u7897 n th\u7853 t tho\u7843 i m\'e1i n\'ean \u273 \'e3 gi\u432 \u7901 ng mua r\u7897 ng m\u7897 t m\'e9t n\u259 m, nh\u432 ng th\u7921 c ra l\'fac ng\u7911  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  chi\u7871 m m\u7897 t n\u7917 a, b\'f3ng \u273 en kia li\u7873 n c\'f4ng khai n\u7857 m th\u7859 ng l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, th\u432 \u7901 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7857 m \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t n\u7855 m tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 n nh\'e0 n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903 . Nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ch\'ecm \u273 \u7855 m trong \u7843 o t\u432 \u7903 ng nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng ra, c\'f2n m\u417  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c m\u417  \u273 \u7865 p r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p t\u7889 t b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Linh ng\uc0\u7885 c v\u7899 i b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7921 ng tro c\u7889 t c\'f9ng \u273 eo tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7917  l\u7845 y linh ng\u7885 c xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7875  v\'e0o ng\u259 n k\'e9p trong c\u7863 p c\'f4ng v\u259 n, ch\u7881  \u273 eo b\'ecnh s\u7913 , th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7847 m c\u7863 p c\'f4ng v\u259 n, m\u7885 i th\u7913  c\u361 ng v\u7851 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec ph\'e1t sinh. V\'ec v\u7853 y c\u7853 u c\'e0ng th\'eam y\'ean t\'e2m l\u7899 n m\u7853 t, c\u7845 t linh ng\u7885 c v\'e0o trong ng\u259 n k\'e9o t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t ng\'e0y ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t th\'e1ng 11, b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7845 p ba T\u7915  Giang c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7865 n c\u7853 u \u273 i ch\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  v\'f9ng kh\'e1c, T\u7915  Giang th\'ec l\u7841 i l\'ean T\'f4 D\'e2n h\u7885 c \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, h\u7885 c ch\'ednh quy xong th\'ec ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7885 c ti\u7871 n s\u297  lu\'f4n \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f3, n\u417 i h\u7855 n h\u7865 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng g\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c T\'f4 D\'e2n n\u7857 m \u7903  g\u7847 n ngo\u7841 i th\'e0nh, nghe n\'f3i \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  m\'e1i nh\'e0 l\u7847 u d\u7841 y h\u7885 c s\u7869  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\'e1nh \u273 \u7891 ng l\'faa v\'e0ng r\u7921 c r\u7905 . C\'e1ch tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c kh\'f4ng xa l\'e0 h\u7891  T\'f4 D\'e2n, m\u7863 c d\'f9 l\'e0 h\u7891  nh\'e2n t\u7841 o nh\u432 ng di\u7879 n t\'edch kh\'e1 l\u7899 n, n\u432 \u7899 c h\u7891  \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng s\'e2u, h\u417 n n\u7919 a nghe n\'f3i d\'f9 l\'e0 ch\u7895  d\u432 \u7899 i n\u432 \u7899 c g\u7847 n b\u7901  th\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 b\'f9n nh\'e3o, ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng r\u7845 t kh\'f3 c\u7913 u l\'ean, nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng x\u7843 y ra kh\'f4ng \'edt chuy\u7879 n, c\'f3 tr\u432 \u7907 t ch\'e2n, c\u361 ng c\'f3 c\u7889  \'fd t\'ecm ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 T\uc0\u7915  Giang th\u7901 i c\u7845 p ba r\u7845 t th\'e2n thi\u7871 t, sau khi \u259 n xong li\u7873 n \u273 i d\u7885 c c\u7845 p ba.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c v\'f4 c\'f9ng ti\'eau \u273 i\u7873 u, th\u7921 c v\u7853 t b\'ean h\u7891  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  n\'ean kh\'f4 h\'e9o, gi\'f3 x\'e0o x\u7841 c, c\'f3 ch\'fat c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\'ea l\u432 \u417 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o gi\'f3 \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\u7841 nh, v\u7915 a \u273 \u7883 nh n\'f3i t\'ecm qu\'e1n c\'e0 ph\'ea n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 g\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0o ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ch\u7907 t th\u7845 y T\u7915  Giang v\u432 \u417 n c\u7893  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 ang nh\'ecn g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn theo \'e1nh m\uc0\u7855 t h\u7855 n, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y h\u7891  b\'ean kia c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m \u273 \'f4ng \u273 ang v\'e2y th\'e0nh v\'f2ng tr\'f2n, c\'f2n c\'f3 xe c\u7843 nh s\'e1t v\u7899 i xe c\u7913 u th\u432 \u417 ng \u7903  \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t h\u417 i: "L\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y th\'edch tham gia n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t, m\u7863 c k\u7879  chuy\u7879 n t\u7889 t hay x\u7845 u \u273 \u7873 u mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n xem m\u7897 t ch\'fat, tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u417 n ph\'e2n n\u7917 a l\'e0 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng may, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u432 \u7899 c nhanh \u273 i sang b\'ean \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u l\'e0 m\u7885 i khi, lo\u7841 i n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7889 n c\'f2n kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p, tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n. Nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ta v\u7851 n n\'f3i t\u7915  s\u432 \u7899 ng th\'e0nh kh\u7893  th\'ec kh\'f3 quen ch\u7913  kh\u7893  th\'e0nh s\u432 \u7899 ng th\'ec d\u7877  quen, th\u7901 i gian ba th\'e1ng n\'e0y, l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng v\u7851 n g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i b\'f3ng d\'e1ng m\u7897 t hai ng\u432 \u7901 i k\u7923  qu\'e1i nh\u432  \u273 \'eam t\u7915  Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  tr\u7903  v\u7873 , ho\u7863 c l\'e0 \u273 \'f4i khi b\u7883  \'e1c m\u7897 ng qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u, nh\u432 ng th\u7901 i gian th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'e0ng l\'e2u, t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng hi\u7879 n r\'f5, v\u7853 y m\'e0 m\u7897 t ch\'fat chuy\u7879 n qu\u7927  qu\'e1i l\'e0m lo\u7841 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i, tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  y\'ean l\u7863 ng an \u7893 n, d\'f9 l\'e0 l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 linh ng\u7885 c th\u7911  h\u7897  k\'e8m v\u7899 i l\'fac \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u7903  c\'f9ng m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m thanh ni\'ean tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed d\u7891 i d\'e0o c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7853 m ch\'ed \u273 \'f4i khi khi\u7871 n cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ho\'e0i nghi h\u417 n hai m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m \u273 \'e3 qua l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 th\u7853 t hay huy\u7877 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n nay ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f3 cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng an \u7893 n, trong ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 d\u7847 n th\u7843  l\u7887 ng ph\'f2ng b\u7883  trong l\'f2ng, b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u361 ng theo T\u7915  Giang \u273 i qua b\'ean kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean m\uc0\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t n\u7857 m m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, n\u7917 a th\'e2n ph\u7911  k\'edn v\u7843 i tr\u7855 ng, m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 chuy\'ean gia \u273 ang ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t tra x\'e9t g\'ec \u273 \'f3, t\u7915  g\'f3c \u273 \u7897  n\'e0y c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn qua v\u7915 a v\u7863 n th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'e2n th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  b\u7883  ng\'e2m n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i ph\'f9 th\u361 ng tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat ch\'f3p m\u361 i b\u7903 i v\'ec l\u7897  ra kh\u7887 i m\u7863 t n\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 l\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7887  l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang li\u7871 c m\u7897 t c\'e1i li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn n\u7919 a, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean lui ra ph\'eda sau, mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "Ch\'fang ta \u273 i th\'f4i \u273 i th\'f4i, \'e0i, t\u7899  th\u7853 t l\'e0, nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p l\u7841 i qu\'ean m\u7845 t c\u7853 u gan nh\u7887  nh\u7845 t, h\u7891 i c\u7845 p ba \u7845 y m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7889 n th\u7853 t xa, ngay c\u7843  chuy\u7879 n ma c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nghe."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 thi\u7871 u nam thi\u7871 u n\u7919  \u273 ang \u273 \u7897  tu\u7893 i ng\u7853 p tr\'e0n l\'f2ng hi\u7871 u k\u7923 , \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7845 y lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n th\u7847 n th\u7847 n qu\u7927  qu\u7927  \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7913 ng th\'fa, ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng gi\u7843 i tr\'ed so v\u7899 i b\u7885 n nh\u7887  b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u361 ng ng\'e2y th\u417  h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u, t\u7909  h\u7885 p c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895  m\u7903  h\u7897 i k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n ma, ch\u417 i b\'fat ti\'ean hay \u273 \u297 a ti\'ean c\'e1c loa\u803 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng l\'e0m h\u7871 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng b\u7883  l\'f4i k\'e9o \u273 \u7871 n h\u7897 i k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n ma m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c s\u7889 t ba ng\'e0y, sau \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng bao gi\u7901  tham gia ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng n\'e0y n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297  th\u7853 t ra kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u nh\'e1t gan, l\u7847 n ph\'e1t s\u7889 t kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0 v\'ec s\u7907  qu\'e1 m\u7913 c, l\'fac \u7845 y b\u7885 n c\u7853 u m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m h\u7885 c sinh ng\u7891 i v\'e2y quanh m\u7897 t ch\u7895  k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n ma, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\'ecnh m\'f2 \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t m\'e3nh li\u7879 t, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\u7841 i m\u417  h\u7891  th\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng b\u7885 n c\u7853 u c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\'f2ng "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng c\u361 ng \u273 ang l\u7859 ng l\u7863 ng nghe.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng b\'e0 ngo\uc0\u7841 i c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t l\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i sau khi nghe chuy\u7879 n xong li\u7873 n nghi\'eam kh\u7855 c qu\u7903  m\u7855 ng c\u7853 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n b\'e0 v\'ec b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng m\'ecnh m\'e0 t\'e2m s\u7913 c lao l\u7921 c qu\'e1 \u273 \u7897 , trong l\'f2ng \'e1y n\'e1y, t\u7915  sau l\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 h\'e0nh x\u7917  c\'e0ng th\'eam c\u7849 n th\u7853 n, r\u7901 i xa t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u m\'e0 n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c coi nh\u432  l\'e0 "T\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7871 t".\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng may t\'ecnh h\'ecnh b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 t\u7889 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 ang suy ngh\u297 , b\u7883  T\u7915  Giang k\'e9o m\u7897 t ph\'e1t c\u361 ng quay ng\u432 \u7901 i chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 i, \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang nh\'ecn m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u thu\u7853 n theo tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c nh\'ecn qua, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang v\'e2y xem kia c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i", ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  to\'e0n th\'e2n tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch ph\'f9 th\u361 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat ch\'f3p m\u361 i l\'e0 \u273 \u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7855 n" \u273 ang nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\'e1t l\uc0\u7841 nh, v\'f4 th\u7913 c s\u7901  l\'ean linh ng\u7885 c tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 th\'f3i quen \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 y n\u259 m qua c\u7911 a c\u7853 u\'97\'97 nh\u432 ng trong tay l\u7841 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  l\'e0 th\'e2n th\u7875  h\u432  nh\u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng nh\'e3n *th\'f4ng linh gi\u7843  nh\u432  trong truy\u7879 n hay phim, d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ma qu\u7927 , th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7843 n th\'e2n t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i suy y\u7871 u ho\u7863 c \u7903  v\'e0o ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t m\u7899 i h\u417 i th\u7845 y b\'f3ng d\'e1ng l\u7901  m\u7901 , m\'e0 t\u7915  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 n th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y r\'f5 nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 nh\u432  th\u7871  ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\u7879  \'97\'97 th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t \u273 \u7871 n c\u7853 u. B\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng d\u432 \u7899 i lo\u7841 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng n\'e0y th\u7913  kia s\u7869  b\'e1m theo c\u7853 u, v\u7873  ph\u7847 n b\'e1m bao l\'e2u, c\'f3 th\u432 \u417 ng t\u7893 n c\u7853 u hay kh\'f4ng, \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t kh\'f3 n\'f3i.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (th\'f4ng linh gi\uc0\u7843 : ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'e2u th\'f4ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Khi c\'f2n nh\uc0\u7887  m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 o s\u297  c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng b\'e1i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, ch\'fang l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  ch\u7845 p ni\u7879 m r\u7845 t s\'e2u, m\u7897 t khi ch\'fang \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u, mu\u7889 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c nh\u7901  xin gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng. C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  th\'e0nh qu\u7927 , nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia l\'e0 s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i ti\'eau c\u7921 c l\u7841 i r\u7845 t t\'e0 m\'f4n, tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7841 i \u273 a s\u7889  c\'e1i g\u7885 i l\'e0 "Qu\u7927  qu\'e1i" \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i sau khi ch\u7871 t bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh, m\'e0 ch\u7881  l\'e0 h\u432 \u7903 ng nh\'e2n kh\'ed, m\u432 \u7907 n h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 th\'f4i. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7921 c k\u7923  t\'e0 t\'ednh ho\u7863 c o\'e1n kh\'ed r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng m\u7899 i c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng c\u7921 c th\u7845 p h\'f3a th\'e0nh qu\u7927  qu\'e1i, c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i nh\'e2n gian d\'e0i l\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'e1i l\uc0\u7841 i, con ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 "linh h\u7891 n" l\u432 u l\u7841 i, Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\'fac nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i "linh h\u7891 n" nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  l\u7841 i \'e2m th\u7847 m b\u7843 o v\u7879  nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  c\u7853 u. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 "linh h\u7891 n" v\u7899 i b\u7843 n th\u7875  \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n li\'ean quan, gi\u7889 ng m\u7897 t d\u7841 ng di v\u7853 t \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i t\'f3m l\uc0\u7841 i, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia v\u7889 n l\'e0 t\'e0 t\'ednh, sau khi b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec kh\u7843  n\u259 ng ra tay h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e0ng l\u7899 n, nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c t\u7915 ng tr\u7843 i qua l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u7853 u \'e2m th\u7847 m h\u7889 i h\u7853 n trong l\'f2ng, m\u7855 ng m\'ecnh t\u7921  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7871 t, kh\'f4ng n\'ean t\u7899 i g\u7847 n m\u7845 y lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n \u7891 n \'e0o n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng h\u7889 i h\u7853 n c\u361 ng v\'f4 \'edch. Nh\'e1y m\u7855 t s\u7901  l\'ean b\'ecnh s\u7913  m\u7899 i nh\u7899  t\u7899 i linh ng\u7885 c \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  m\'ecnh c\u7845 t v\'e0o t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, m\u7845 y ng\'e0y nay \u273 \u7873 u d\u7921 a v\'e0o tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi che ch\u7903 , nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  v\'ec sao l\u7847 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng b\u7843 o v\u7879  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
