\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia h\'ecnh nh\u432  ch\'fa \'fd th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn l\u7841 i n\'f3, v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\'e1ch qua \u273 \'e1m \u273 \'f4ng chen ch\'fac, b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n t\u7853 p t\u7877 nh nh\u432 ng c\u7921 c k\u7923  nhanh \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m quay ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i, ch\u7881  d\'f9ng tay ph\u7843 i k\'e9o c\'e1nh tay T\u7915  Giang lui v\u7873  ph\'eda sau theo bi\'ean \u273 \u7897  nh\u7887 , tay tr\'e1i g\u7855 t gao si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t b\'ecnh s\u7913  tr\'ean c\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia \u273 i qua ch\u7895  n\'e0o li\u7873 n \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i d\u7845 u ch\'e2n d\'ednh n\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i xung quanh l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t gi\'e1c ra, ch\u7881  c\'f3 T\u7915  Giang ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng, h\u7887 i c\u7853 u: "Sao th\u7871 ? Kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u. D\'e2n gian v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u7891 n \u273 \u7841 i chuy\u7879 n qu\u7927  n\u432 \u7899 c t\'ecm k\u7867  ch\u7871 t thay, c\u7853 u s\u7907  m\'ecnh b\u7883  th\u7913  n\'e0y qu\u7845 n l\'ean, s\u7907  l\'fac r\u7917 a m\u7863 t c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng t\u7915  ph\'eda sau s\u7869  du\u7895 i ra m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i b\'e0n tay \u7845 n m\u7863 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh xu\u7889 ng b\u7891 n r\u7917 a, ng\u7841 t n\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Mu\uc0\u7889 n tr\'e1nh th\u7913  n\'e0y, ch\u7881  d\u7921 a v\'e0o vi\u7879 c ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tr\u7889 n n\u7893 i, n\u7871 u v\u7853 t kia \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t \u273 \u7871 n c\u7853 u, b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7899 i T\u7915  Giang c\'f3 tr\u7889 n nhanh h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u361 ng v\'f4 d\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 t kia c\'f9ng l\u7855 m ch\u7881  c\'f2n c\'e1ch c\u7853 u n\u259 m b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7917 i th\u7845 y m\'f9i n\u432 \u7899 c tanh t\u432 \u7903 i v\'e0 m\'f9i h\'f4i th\u7889 i, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'ed t\u7913 c \u7849 m \u432 \u7899 t \'e2m l\'e3nh. C\u7853 u c\u7847 m b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  che \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, trong \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i kh\'f4ng c\'f2n b\u7845 t c\u7913  suy ngh\u297  g\'ec n\u7919 a. Th\u7901 i gian gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng, c\u7843 nh h\u7891 , \u273 \'e1m \u273 \'f4ng, T\u7915  Giang, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh h\'ecnh \u7843 nh \u273 en tr\u7855 ng; c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c T\u7915  Giang h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y mi\u7879 ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \'f4\u803 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng tr\u7889 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7847 n n\'e0y, v\u7853 y th\'ec th\u7915 a d\u7883 p tr\u7901 i ch\u432 a t\u7889 i, c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i nhanh ch\'f3ng l\'ean n\'fai T\'e2y Thanh c\u7847 u c\u7913 u, nh\u432 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  c\'f2n kh\'f4ng tr\u7845 n \'e1p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t li\u7879 u Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng c\'f3 c\'f2n bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p n\'e0o kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y, th\u7913  kia \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7845 t c\u7913  d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u n\'e0o, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng g\'ec v\u7915 a r\u7891 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ch\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c do c\u7853 u sinh ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'e1i ph\uc0\u7843 i quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn, th\u7901 i gian tr\'f4i qua m\u7897 t l\'e1t, xe c\u7843 nh s\'e1t v\'e0 xe c\u7913 u th\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i \u273 i, thi th\u7875  nguy\'ean b\u7843 n \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y n\u7919 a, qu\u7847 n ch\'fang v\'e2y xem ch\u432 a t\u7843 n \u273 i v\u7851 n \u273 ang x\'ec x\'e0o b\'e0n t\'e1n v\u7873  h\u7891  n\u432 \u7899 c, m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 i th\'fac trung ni\'ean v\u7915 a \u273 \u7849 y xe h\u7841 t d\u7867  rang \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\u7915 a rao l\u7899 n, tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y t\u7915 ng \u273 o\'e0n t\u7915 ng \u273 o\'e0n h\u7885 c sinh c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f9a \u273 \u7841 p xe \u273 \u7841 p \u273 i ngang qua \'97\'97 h\u7871 t th\u7843 y \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7847 m b\'ecnh s\u7913  d\'e1n l\'ean m\'f4i kh\u7869  ch\u7841 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\'edn \u273 \u7891  h\'f4n th\u7853 p t\u7921  gi\'e1, c\'f3 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i nh\u7865  nh\'f5m gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  s\u7889 ng s\'f3t sau tai n\u7841 n, sau \u273 \'f3 th\u7843  l\u7841 i b\'ecnh s\u7913  v\u7873  ch\u7895  c\u361 . B\'ecnh s\u7913  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u \u273 eo tr\'ean c\u7893 , \u273 \u432 \u7907 c truy\u7873 n nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  t\u7915  c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u, mang theo m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u7845 m \'e1p, l\'fac n\'e0y b\u7883  gi\'f3 thu \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\u7893 i l\'ean th\u7893 i qua, l\'fac th\u7843  tr\u7903  v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c tr\u7903  n\'ean r\u7845 t l\u7841 nh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o \u273 ang vu\u7889 t ve c\u7853 u, l\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean run c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m qu\u7927  n\u432 \u7899 c bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t \u7903  \u273 \u7857 ng kia, ph\'eda sau c\u7853 u xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0u \u273 en. B\'f3ng \u273 en im l\u7863 ng \'f4m c\u7853 u, tay tr\'e1i \u273 \u432 a ra ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c v\'f2ng l\'ean eo c\u7853 u, tay ph\u7843 i v\'f2ng qua tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, \'f4m c\u7893  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 em c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u kh\u7843 m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang \u273 \u432 a tay xua xua tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 ? V\u7915 a r\u7891 i l\'e0m sao th\u7871 ? Tr\'fang t\'e0 \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean vung tay m\uc0\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 \u7849 y tay h\u7855 n ra: "C\u7909 c t\u7849 y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng c\'f3 n\'f3i m\'f2. \u272 i th\'f4i, \u273 \u7871 n qu\'e1n c\'e0 ph\'ea g\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u7903  \u273 \'e2y l\u7841 nh qu\'e1." D\u7913 t l\u7901 i d\u7853 m ch\'e2n m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang c\u7903 i \'e1o kho\'e1c ngo\'e0i ra \u273 \'f3n gi\'f3: "M\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7841 nh! C\u7853 u y\u7871 u qu\'e1!"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1ch \uc0\u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c T\'f4 D\'e2n kh\'f4ng xa c\'f3 m\u7897 t ti\u7879 m "C\'e0 ph\'ea Xanh", t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7891  u\u7889 ng c\'e0 ph\'ea n\u432 \u7899 c tr\'e1i c\'e2y b\'ean trong \u273 \u7873 u nh\u7841 t nh\u7869 o v\'f4 c\'f9ng, r\u7845 t v\'f4 v\u7883 , nh\u432 ng b\'e1nh c\'e0 r\u7889 t ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 \u259 n r\u7845 t ngon, c\u7917 a ti\u7879 m kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chia l\'e0m hai t\u7847 ng, trang tr\'ed tao nh\'e3 \u7845 m \'e1p, l\u7841 i m\u7903  \u7903  g\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c, c\u7843  ng\'e0y l\'e0m \u259 n r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng t\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang l\'e0 kh\'e1ch quen c\u7911 a ti\u7879 m n\'e0y, c\'f3 l\'e0m th\u7867  h\u7897 i vi\'ean, h\u7855 n d\u7851 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i v\'e0o, v\u7915 a \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a ra li\u7873 n c\'f3 m\u7897 t lu\u7891 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'ed \u7845 m \'e1p ph\u7843  \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, c\'f2n c\'f3 m\'f9i th\u417 m c\u7911 a c\'e0 ph\'ea v\'e0 b\u417 . M\u7863 t ti\u7873 n c\u7917 a ti\u7879 m b\'e0i tr\'ed r\u7845 t \u273 \u7865 p, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\u7897 ng r\'e3i v\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ri\'eang t\u432  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, gi\'e0n hoa, t\u7911  s\'e1ch b\'e1o, c\'e1c lo\u7841 i v\u7853 t d\u7909 ng trang tr\'ed k\u7871 t h\u7907 p v\u7899 i s\'f4 pha \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\u7871 p \u273 \u7863 t kh\'e9o l\'e9o khi\u7871 n cho m\u7895 i b\'e0n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng b\'e0n kh\'e1c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7863 t m\'ecnh v\'e0o trong kh\'f4ng gian \u273 \u7897 c l\u7853 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ti\uc0\u7879 m nu\'f4i hai con m\'e8o, m\u7897 t con m\'e0u v\'e0ng m\u7897 t con \u273 en tr\u7855 ng, T\u7915  Giang quen thu\u7897 c ti\u7871 n l\u7841 i g\u7847 n ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m xu\u7889 ng \'f4m m\'e8o si\u7871 t v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c: "\u272 \u7841 i Hoa, Nh\u7883  Hoa, nh\u7899  tao kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh h\u7855 n: "Hai con m\'e8o n\'e0y t\'ean l\'e0 \u272 \u7841 i Hoa Nh\u7883  Hoa??"\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i, m\u7897 t con t\'ean Monday m\u7897 t con t\'ean Friday, t\'ean ch\u7859 ng th\'e2n th\u432 \u417 ng g\'ec h\u7871 t, c\u7913  nh\u432  Robinson ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7843 o hoang \u7845 y. \u272 \u7841 i Hoa Nh\u7883  Hoa l\'e0 t\u7899  \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u7845 y, hay h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean y\'eau th\'edch ng\uc0\u7891 i x\u7893 m xu\u7889 ng, mu\u7889 n s\u7901  s\u7901  Th\u7913  S\'e1u tr\'f2n vo b\u7883  g\u7885 i l\'e0 Nh\u7883  Hoa, ai ng\u7901  con m\'e8o \u273 en tr\u7855 ng tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn b\'e9o m\u7853 p l\u7841 i r\u7845 t linh ho\u7841 t c\u7845 p t\u7889 c nh\u7843 y ra ngo\'e0i, ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng l\'ean l\u7847 u, ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m \u7903  kh\'fac quanh c\u7847 u thang, hai m\u7855 t gi\u432 \u417 ng l\'ean h\u7871 t s\u7913 c \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  Hai sau khi b\u7883  T\u7915  Giang \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c t\u7899 i g\u7847 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean c\u7921 c k\u7923  b\u7845 t an, d\u7889 c s\u7913 c li\u7873 u m\u7841 ng tr\u7889 n ra kh\u7887 i ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n nh\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng sang ch\u7895  kh\'e1c tr\u7889 n ph\'eda sau s\'f4 pha, m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e8o \u273 \u7891 ng d\u7841 ng \'e2m u nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang quay sang nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, ai th\'e1n: "\u272 \u7841 i Hoa c\u7911 a t\u7899 ! Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u th\u7871  n\'e0o l\u7841 i bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh m\'e8o ch\'ea ch\'f3 kh\'f4ng \u432 a th\u7871  h\u7843 , \u272 \u7841 i Hoa Nh\u7883  Hoa r\u7845 t d\u7841 n ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng b\u7883  c\u7853 u d\u7885 a ch\u7841 y r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'f4 t\u7897 i: "T\u7899  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t a."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7853 u kh\'ed ch\u7845 t \'f4n h\'f2a, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7883  \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t nh\u7887  ch\'e1n gh\'e9t. Nh\u432 ng t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh ch\'f3 m\'e8o nh\u7887  th\u7845 y c\u7853 u li\u7873 n b\u7887  ch\u7841 y nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng x\u7843 y ra\'97\'97 \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u b\u7883  th\u7913  kh\'f4ng s\u7841 ch s\u7869  qu\u7845 n l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd ngh\uc0\u297  n\'e0y ch\u7881  xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  c\u7853 u v\u7913 t b\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Hi\uc0\u7879 n gi\u7901  b\u7889 n ph\'eda xung quanh kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\'ecnh m\'f2, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1c \'fd \'e2m l\'e3nh, t\u7915  khi mang theo tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u li\u7873 n tr\u7903  n\'ean s\u7841 ch s\u7869  t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7899 i nay ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i trong ti\u7879 m kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m, T\u7915  Giang c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'ean l\u7847 u hai, ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng s\'f4 pha b\u7889 n ch\u7895  m\'e0u kem \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh gi\'e0n hoa. Th\u7913  S\'e1u m\'e0u \u273 en tr\u7855 ng ngay l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7845 t b\u432 \u7899 c l\'ean l\u7847 u, trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ho\u7843 ng s\u7907  c\u7845 p t\u7889 c ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\'f3ng d\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang t\u7921  quy\u7871 t g\u7885 i m\u7897 t b\'ecnh c\'e0 ph\'ea, hai mi\u7871 ng b\'e1nh c\'e0 r\u7889 t. C\'e0 ph\'ea v\u7851 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n nh\u7841 t nh\u7869 o v\'f4 v\u7883  nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi, b\'e1nh c\'e0 r\u7889 t d\'f9ng c\'e0 r\u7889 t b\'e0o th\u7853 t nh\u7887  c\'f9ng v\u7899 i h\u7841 t \'f3c ch\'f3, c\'e1c lo\u7841 i h\u7841 t kh\'f4 l\'e0m th\'e0nh, ph\'eda tr\'ean ph\u7911  l\'ean m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng ph\'f4 mai v\u7883  qu\'fdt th\u7853 t d\'e0y, chua chua ng\u7885 t ngo\u803 t m\u7873 m tan.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang \u273 \u432 a tay r\'f3t c\'e0 ph\'ea cho m\'ecnh v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, ch\u7895  tr\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n t\u7889 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" \u273 ang ng\u7891 i ch\u7881 nh t\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, Th\u7913  S\'e1u ch\u7841 y l\'ean l\u7847 u l\'fac n\'e3y \u273 ang gi\u7845 u m\'ecnh \u7903  m\u7897 t g\'f3c ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i gi\'e0n hoa, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n g\u7855 t gao nh\'ecn b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\'ean n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f4i khi \u273 \'fang l\'e0 kh\'f4ng nh\u7841 y c\u7843 m b\u7857 ng \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 p m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m c\'e0 ph\'ea, d\'f9ng th\'eca b\u7841 c nh\u7887  m\'fac m\u7897 t ch\'fat ph\'f4 mai ph\'eda tr\'ean b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t, v\'f4 th\u7913 c du\u7895 i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i ra li\u7871 m li\u7871 m \'97\'97 \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 th\'f3i quen t\u7915  nh\u7887  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u l\'fac \u259 n m\'f3n n\'e0y, nghe n\'f3i l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec thi\u7871 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c an to\'e0n. C\'e1i "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" kia v\u7851 n lu\'f4n chuy\'ean ch\'fa nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t, *nh\'e2n t\'ednh h\u417 i thay \u273 \u7893 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (n\'f4m na l\'e0 tr\uc0\u7903  n\'ean gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang n\u7917 a mi\u7871 ng b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t \u273 \'e3 v\'e0o b\u7909 ng, trong l\'fac b\u7853 n r\u7897 n ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u tr\u7915 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867  c\u7853 u \u259 n nhanh l\'ean."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'f2ng t\uc0\u7921  nh\u7911 , v\u7889 n l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u7875  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n m\'e0, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i v\u7897 i, v\'ec v\u7853 y l\u7841 i \u273 i\u7873 m t\u297 nh m\'fac m\u7897 t th\'eca ph\'f4 mai, d\'f9ng \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m li\u7871 m cu\u7889 n v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  s\'e1p \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n, tay \u273 \'e8 ch\u7863 t sau g\'e1y Tr\'ec Di\'ean, kh\u7869  li\u7871 m l\'ean \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bu\'f4ng th\'eca b\uc0\u7841 c xu\u7889 ng, nh\u7845 p m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m c\'e0 ph\'ea: "Sao h\'f4m nay ph\'f4 mai l\u7841 i h\u417 i l\u7841 nh nh\u7881 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang \u273 \'e3 \u259 n b\'e1nh xong, \u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t m\u7901  m\u7883 t ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u: "T\u7899  c\'f3 th\u7845 y l\u7841 nh \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
