\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang \u259 n xong nh\u7899  t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n: "Tr\'ec Di\'ean, m\u7907  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n mu\u7889 n gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u ch\'e1u g\'e1i b\'e0 \u7845 y cho c\u7853 u \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 ," Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, "H\u417 n n\u7919 a l\u7847 n n\'e0y ch\'fa t\u7899  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd \u273 \u7875  t\u7899  quay v\u7873  g\u7863 p, t\u7915  ch\u7889 i kh\'f4ng ti\u7879 n." D\'f9 sao t\'ednh ra c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f2n ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fa n\'e0y l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n, g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng may c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c b\u7853 n r\u7897 n vi\u7879 n c\u7899  kh\'f4ng xin ngh\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  ch\u7889 i, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m m\u7899 i ch\'fa nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  g\u7885 i c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873  t\u7843 o m\u7897  th\u7855 p h\u432 \u417 ng cho \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ti\u7879 n \u273 \'f9n \u273 \u7849 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa v\'e0 m\uc0\u7907  c\u7853 u quen nhau khi \u273 ang c\'f4ng t\'e1c, so v\u7899 i ch\'fa, \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n nh\'e0 m\u7907  t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 nh\'e0 c\'f3 ti\u7873 n g\u7917 i ng\'e2n h\'e0ng, c\'f2n c\'f3 c\u7893  phi\u7871 u trong c\'f4ng ty ch\'fa, n\u259 ng l\u7921 c di\u7879 n m\u7841 o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng k\'e9m, m\u7907  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\u7889  \'fd t\'e1c h\u7907 p c\u7853 u v\u7899 i ch\'e1u g\'e1i m\'ecnh, ch\'fa Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\'f3 ch\'fat ch\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7855 t \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n c\'f4 ch\'e1u g\'e1i kia, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng x\u7913 ng v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng t\u7887  th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  g\'ec, v\u7873  sau th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p kh\'f4ng quen b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u g\'ec li\'ean quan, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'ecnh v\u7899 i t\u432  c\'e1ch tr\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7889 i duy nh\u7845 t n\'ean thay c\u7853 u \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m, l\u7841 i li\'ean t\u7909 c b\u7883  v\u7907  k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i tho\'e1ng ra m\u7863 t k\'eau Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7863 p m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, xem c\'f3 h\u7907 p duy\'ean hay kh\'f4ng, kh\'f4ng h\u7907 p th\'ec l\u7841 i t\'ednh c\'e1i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u quay v\u7873  \u273 i g\u7863 p c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao, ch\'fang ta c\u361 ng l\u7899 n \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nh\u7887  g\'ec n\u7919 a, n\'ean suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nghe c\u7853 u m\u7907  an b\'e0i a, b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'f2n l\'e0 nh\'ecn th\u7917  xem c\'f3 h\u7907 p \'fd hay kh\'f4ng, sang n\u259 m s\u7869  l\'e0 \u273 i kh\u7855 p n\u417 i xem m\u7863 t, qua hai n\u259 m n\u7919 a li\u7873 n bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh "M\u7907  th\u7845 y \u273 \u7915 ng k\'e9n ch\u7885 n n\u7919 a, L\'e2m mu\u7897 i c\u7911 a con r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, t\'ecm ng\'e0y \u273 i \u273 \u259 ng k\'ed k\u7871 t h\'f4n \u273 i", c\u7853 u n\'f3i xem c\'f3 toi \u273 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, ch\uc0\u7907 t nghe T\u7915  Giang ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 t\u7899  c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng tr\'e1ch c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ch\u7895  c\u7853 u l\'e0m ba n\u259 m kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y n\u7893 i m\u7897 t sinh v\u7853 t kh\'e1c ph\'e1i. Th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 i, t\u7899  gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u cho c\u7853 u hai ti\u7875 u h\u7885 c mu\u7897 i l\'e0m quen m\u7897 t ch\'fat. H\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'e9 l\u7899 p d\u432 \u7899 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p chung h\u7891 i c\u7845 p ba c\u7911 a ch\'fang ta li\u7873 n khen c\u7853 u \u273 \u7865 p trai, t\u7899  n\'f3i gi\u7905 n b\u7843 o \u273 \u7875  t\u7899  gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u cho, b\'e9 \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297  d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed nam gi\u7899 i m\u7899 i \u273 \u7911  \u273 \u7875  tr\u7845 n qu\u7927  a, n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 ch\u7885 n \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c ch\u7885 n khoa, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u c\u7889  \'fd ch\u7885 n \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c L\'fd C\'f4ng khoa h\'f2a th\u432 \u7907 ng n\u7893 i danh t\u7881  l\u7879  nam n\u7919  t\'e1m ch\u7885 i m\u7897 t, sau khi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng l\'e0 nam nhi\u7873 u n\u7919  \'edt. T\u7915  Giang th\'ec kh\'e1c, ti\u7871 n s\u297  T\u7915  h\u7885 c khoa x\'e3 h\u7897 i h\u7885 c, khoa h\u7855 n tuy\u7875 n n\u7919  v\'e0o \u273 \u7873 u ba ch\u7885 n m\u7897 t, T\u7915  Giang n\'f3i d\'f9 h\u7855 n c\'f3 h\u7911 y dung c\u361 ng v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  *n\u7857 m th\u7855 ng.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (n\uc0\u7857 m th\u7855 ng: kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7855 ng)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 n hai m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m lu\'f4n s\u7889 ng trong n\u417 m n\u7899 p lo s\u7907 , th\u7901 i th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c kh\u7855 c lu\'f4n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u259 n b\u7919 a nay lo b\u7919 a mai, ngay c\u7843  m\u7841 ng s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\u361 ng l\'e0 c\u7843  m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , c\'e0ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'e2n nh\u259 \u769 c \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n l\u7845 y v\u7907  sinh con, tuy c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p n\u7919  h\'e0i t\u7917  tho\'e1ng l\u7897  v\u7867  h\u7843 o c\u7843 m v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng chung quy c\u7853 u d\'f9 ch\u7881  \u7903  c\u7841 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i ta th\'f4i c\u361 ng t\u7921  nhi\'ean s\u7869  li\'ean l\u7909 y \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ta, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 \u7873 u \'e2m th\u7847 m xa c\'e1ch h\u7885 . H\u417 n n\u7917 a \u273 \u7901 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 chia ra ph\'e2n n\u7917 a tinh l\u7921 c ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n giao du k\u7871 t b\u7841 n v\'e0 chuy\u7879 n t\'ecnh c\u7843 m \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m g\'ec, b\'e2y gi\u7901  nghe T\u7915  Giang n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7855 n n\'f3i r\u7845 t c\'f3 l\'fd. Ch\'fa c\u361 ng l\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng m\'ecnh c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n, n\u7871 u t\u7921  m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh th\'edch, ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \'e9p bu\u7897 c m\'ecnh tr\u7903  v\u7873  k\u7871 t th\'e2n. \u272 \'e3 c\'f3 tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  che ch\u7903 , t\'ednh m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh t\u7841 m th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7841 i, n\u7871 u v\u7853 y c\'f3 ph\u7843 i m\'ecnh c\u361 ng n\'ean t\'ednh to\'e1n \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n s\u7889 ng cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng hay kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7849 n th\u7853 n c\'e2n nh\u7855 c m\u7897 t ch\'fat, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i T\u7915  Giang.\cb1 \
