\cf2 \cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  b\u7843 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 a Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n n\u7845 u c\u417 m c\u361 ng l\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i mua th\u7913 c \u259 n, b\u7919 a tr\u432 a li\u7873 n \u259 n m\'ec g\'f3i \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, theo th\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7879  d\'e0nh m\u7897 t b\'e1t nh\u7887  cho b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. B\u7903 i v\u7853 y bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u \u273 \'f3i b\u7909 ng s\u7899 m, g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u7891  \u259 n ngo\'e0i \u7903  c\u7917 a ti\u7879 m g\u7847 n nh\'e0 hay \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u259 m gi\u7901  c\u7853 u g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, l\'fac \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i l\'e0 b\u7843 y gi\u7901 , ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  m\'e0u cam bao ph\u7911  ch\'e2n tr\u7901 i ph\'eda xa, s\u7855 c tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n tr\u7847 m tr\u7903  n\'ean t\u7889 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7889 n \u273 ang d\u7885 n d\u7865 p nh\'e0, nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a \u273 o\'e1n l\'e0 \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ch\u7841 y \u273 i m\u7903  c\u7917 a. C\u7853 u m\u7903  c\u7917 a ra m\u7897 t khe nh\u7887 , v\u7915 a \u273 \u7911  \u273 \u7875  nh\'e2n vi\'ean \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7891  v\'e0o, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7853 n l\u7845 y n\'f3i c\'e1m \u417 n, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i \u273 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u417  h\u7891  th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o m\'e0u \u273 en g\u7847 n gi\u7889 ng lo\u7841 i \'e1o phao d\'e1ng d\'e0i, \u273 em m\'ecnh bao l\u7841 i r\u7845 t k\'edn.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi c\uc0\u7847 m \u273 \u7891  \u259 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean b\'e0n \u259 n b\u7887  t\'fai nilon b\'ean ngo\'e0i ra, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i ph\'e1t gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, c\u7853 u th\u432 \u7901 ng mua \u273 \u7891  \u7903  ti\u7879 m kia, bi\u7871 t ti\u7879 m kia \u273 \'f3ng g\'f3i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y, th\u7853 m ch\'ed b\u7845 t k\u7923  c\u7917 a ti\u7879 m n\'e0o c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \'f3ng g\'f3i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y\'97\'97 d\'f9ng gi\u7845 y l\u7909 a hoa m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng ch\u7845 t l\u432 \u7907 ng k\'e9m d\'e1n \u7903  ph\'eda tr\'ean khi\u7871 n cho m\'f3n \u259 n gi\u7889 ng \u273 \u7891  t\u7871  ho\u7863 c l\'e0 \u273 \u7891  c\'fang h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7921 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh, quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i li\u7871 c nh\'ecn b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, l\u7841 y m\u7845 y c\'e1i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n t\'e2m t\'ecnh kh\u7849 u v\u7883  \u259 n c\u417 m. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng m\u7903  gi\u7845 y hoa b\u7885 c c\u417 m h\u7897 p ra m\'e0 b\u7887  l\u7841 i n\'f3 v\'e0o trong t\'fai nilon mang ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a, l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng ra \u273 \u7883 nh g\u7885 i cho ch\u7911  qu\'e1n h\u7887 i xem l\'e0 ch\u7895  n\'e0o g\'e2y ra s\u417  su\u7845 t\'97\'97 \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u m\'e0 n\'f3i, vi\u7879 c l\'e0m n\'e0y thay v\'ec n\'f3i l\'e0 \u273 \'f2i quy\u7873 n l\u7907 i, n\'f3i \u273 \'fang h\u417 n l\'e0 \u273 \u7875  t\'ecm s\u7921  an l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ra nh\'ecn m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u, g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y tr\u7841 m ph\'e1t s\'f3ng khu v\u7921 c n\'e0y lu\'f4n x\u7843 y ra v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng l\u7841 i m\u7845 t t\'edn hi\u7879 u t\u7841 m th\u7901 i, nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o li\'ean h\u7879  v\u7899 i th\u7871  gi\u7899 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\'e0ng l\'e0m t\u259 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t b\u7845 t an trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7855 c tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n t\u7889 i h\u7859 n, t\u7847 m nh\'ecn trong ph\'f2ng tr\u7903  n\'ean l\u7901  m\u7901 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i t\u7899 i c\u7917 a \u7845 n m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, nh\u432 ng \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n tr\u7855 ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng mang \u273 \u7871 n ch\'fat \u7845 m \'e1p n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y ngo\'e0i c\uc0\u7917 a l\u7841 i truy\u7873 n t\u7899 i ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a c\'f3 ti\u7871 t t\u7845 u.\'a0 \'a0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u273 \u7853 p ch\u7853 m m\u7897 t nh\u7883 p. C\u7853 u cau m\'e0y, m\u7903  c\u7917 a g\u7895  b\'ean trong, t\u7915  m\u7855 t m\'e8o tr\'ean c\u7917 a ch\u7889 ng tr\u7897 m nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i \'97\'97 th\u7871  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ai. Trong t\u7847 m m\u7855 t l\'e0 m\u7897 t m\u7843 nh xanh tr\u7855 ng, m\u417  h\u7891  mang theo t\u417  m\'e1u m\'e0u \u273 o\u777 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng m\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e2y \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891 , sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i m\'e3nh li\u7879 t ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec \'97\'97 th\u7913  kia c\u361 ng \u273 ang nh\'ecn v\'e0o trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c lui m\u7841 nh v\u7873  sau hai b\u432 \u7899 c l\u7899 n, su\'fdt ch\'fat n\u7919 a t\'e9 ng\'e3. Sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 em c\u7917 a g\u7895  b\'ean trong \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i th\u7853 t ch\u7863 t, kh\'f3a k\'edn hai t\u7847 ng c\u7917 a nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n, r\u7845 t nhanh r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i huy\u7873 n quan ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng xanh, m\'f4i c\u361 ng v\'f4 th\u7913 c run r\u7849 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a v\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361  vang l\'ean theo nh\u7883 p, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\u7879 t, nghe v\'e0o tai Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ti\u7871 ng b\'f9a \u273 \'f2i m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n th\u7901  m\u7899 i tho\'e1ng \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh t\'e2m tr\u7841 ng, s\u7901  l\'ean b\'ecnh s\u7913  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m v\'e0o b\'e0i v\u7883  vi\u7871 t "Di\u7879 p th\u7883  Ngh\'eanh Chi chi linh" ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang suy ngh\u297  g\'ec \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a b\'ean ngo\'e0i m\u7841 nh l\'ean, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7853 p n\'e1t c\u7917 a. K\u7923  qu\'e1i ch\'ednh l\'e0 ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng l\u7899 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng h\'e0ng x\'f3m l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 kh\'e1ng ngh\u7883  hay ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i di \u273 \u7897 ng ra, v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u, t\'edn hi\u7879 u \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\'e0 t\'edn hi\u7879 u v\'f4 tuy\u7871 n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a, nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c n\'e2ng b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, chui v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , \u273 em c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u361 ng kh\'f3a l\u7841 i th\u7853 t ch\u7863 t, l\u7841 i d\u7901 i t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng qua ch\u7863 n c\u7917 a, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng qu\'ean l\u7845 y ra linh ng\u7885 c t\u7915  trong ng\u259 n k\'e9o \u7903  t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 nh nh\u7841 t r\u7845 t l\'e2u n\u7855 m trong tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m m\u7903  c\u7917 a s\u7893 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  run r\u7849 y k\'e9o ch\u259 n che ph\u7911  ch\'ednh m\'ecnh, tay tr\'e1i n\u7855 m linh ng\u7885 c, \'f4m b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, g\u7855 t gao nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , ch\'fa \'fd nghe ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 "K\'e9t..." m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, l\'e0 ti\u7871 ng c\u7917 a b\'ean ngo\'e0i m\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u417  h\u7891  ngh\u297 , r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f3a c\u7917 a r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ti\uc0\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7913  kia h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c di chuy\u7875 n h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  b\'ean n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n cho\'e1ng v\'e1ng, da g\'e0 t\u7915 ng t\u7847 ng n\u7893 i l\'ean, c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i run r\u7849 y. M\u7863 c d\'f9 khi c\'f2n nh\u7887  t\u7915 ng c\'f3 qu\u7927  qu\'e1i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng m\u432 u h\u7841 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7849 y c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u, nh\u432 ng c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\'f5 r\'e0ng s\u7921  g\u7847 n k\u7873  c\u7911 a th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 v\'e0 n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i khi c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y v\u7851 n l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean. C\u7853 u tho\'e1ng nh\u7899  t\u7899 i truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t d\'e2n gian v\u7851 n hay \u273 \u7891 n \u273 \u7841 i m\'e0 b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i t\u7915 ng k\u7875  cho c\u7853 u nghe\'97\'97 kh\'f4ng n\'ean m\u7903  c\u7917 a cho ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 , kh\'f4ng n\'ean t\'f9y ti\u7879 n m\u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841  v\u7873  nh\'e0, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia ch\u7881  c\u7847 n l\'fac n\'f3 g\'f5 c\u7917 a b\u7841 n m\u7903  c\u7917 a cho n\'f3 m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, l\u7847 n g\'f5 c\u7917 a ti\u7871 p theo kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n b\u7841 n m\u7903  n\'f3 c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean c\uc0\u7853 u m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  v\'f4 th\u7913 c chui v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , ch\u7863 n c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng l\u7841 i. Hy v\u7885 ng th\u7913  kia c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  ng\u259 n l\u7841 i v\'ec hai t\u7847 ng kh\'f4ng gian, hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7873 u vang l\'ean ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , g\u7847 n \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  gh\'e9 v\'e0o l\u7895  tai c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngay c\uc0\u7843  nh\'ecn c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p d\'f9ng ch\u259 n tr\'f9m k\'edn m\'ecnh, t\u7921 a h\u7891  nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 em m\'ecnh ho\'e0n to\'e0n gi\u7845 u \u273 i, gi\u7843  b\u7897  nh\u432  kh\'f4ng t\u7891 n t\u7841 i. C\u7853 u \'f4m b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, to\'e0n th\'e2n ph\'e1t run, n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7843 y \u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t. Trong mi\u7879 ng c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng v\'f4 th\u7913 c l\u7849 m b\u7849 m: "Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Ngh\'eanh Chi... c\u7913 u t\'f4i, c\u7847 u xin ng\'e0i... Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7913 u t\'f4i v\u7899 i... Ngh\'eanh Chi, Ngh\'eanh Chi, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi... xin ng\'e0i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t c\'e2u l\u7849 m b\u7849 m cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng, ngh\u7865 n ng\'e0o trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  che gi\u7845 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7895 i l\u7847 n xem phim kinh d\u7883 , th\u7845 y nh\'e2n v\u7853 t ch\'ednh khi c\'f3 nguy hi\u7875 m \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n li\u7873 n chui v\'e0o trong ch\u259 n c\u7889  g\u7855 ng tr\u7889 n th\u7853 t l\'e0 ngu ng\u7889 c, \u273 \u7871 n khi chuy\u7879 n x\u7843 y ra v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng b\u7843 n n\u259 ng nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean run r\uc0\u7849 y \'f4m b\'e0i v\u7883 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \'f4m l\u7845 y c\u7913 u chu\u7897 c duy nh\u7845 t; \u7903  n\u417 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, m\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en l\u7845 y t\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \u7891 ng d\u7841 ng \'f4m c\u7853 u, \u273 em c\u7853 u d\'e1n v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, c\u7857 m g\u7889 i l\'ean tr\'ean vai c\u7853 u, h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\'f3 ch\'fat vui v\u7867 . Sau \u273 \'f3 ch\u7853 m r\'e3i nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u, th\u432 \u417 ng ti\u7871 c kh\'f4n c\'f9ng li\u7871 m \u273 i v\u7879 t n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t tr\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7853 u b\u7903 i v\'ec ho\u7843 ng s\u7907  qu\'e1 \u273 \u7897  m\'e0 ch\u7843 y ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i c\uc0\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a v\u7851 n \u273 ang ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng b\'f3ng \u273 en l\u7841 i ch\u7881  lo d\'f9ng m\'f4i l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c lau \u273 i n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t tr\'ean m\u7863 t, c\'f2n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng phi\u7873 n l\'f2ng kia b\u7845 t vi s\u7903  \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \

