\cb3 L\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i th\'ec xung quanh tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 s\'e1ng r\u7905 , \'e1nh n\u7855 ng m\'e0u v\'e0ng \u7845 m \'e1p t\u7915  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  chi\u7871 u v\'e0o, chi\u7871 u l\'ean tr\'ean ch\u259 n m\u7873 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7853 t gi\u7853 t th\'e2n th\u7875 , tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c b\u7883  th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 c\u7845 n \u273 \u7871 n \u273 au, c\u7853 u l\u7845 y ra nh\'ecn qua, l\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7845 m b\'e0i v\u7883  m\'e0u \u273 en.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n ph\'e1t sinh chi\u7873 u t\u7889 i h\'f4m qua nhanh ch\'f3ng hi\u7879 n l\'ean, r\'f5 m\u7891 n m\u7897 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, c\u7853 u tr\u7903  m\'ecnh ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, nh\'ecn th\u7845 y t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng v\u7851 n \u273 ang ch\u7863 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7893 i, m\u7903  l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay ra, linh ng\u7885 c c\u361 ng \u273 ang n\u7855 m trong tay \'97\'97 t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u7843 o gi\'e1c, b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ki\u7871 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297  m\'ecnh c\u361 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 v\'f4 lo v\'f4 ngh\u297 , ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua b\u7883  th\u7913  kia g\'f5 c\u7917 a nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7907 t t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7907 t, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  nh\u7899  sau \u273 \'f3 m\'ecnh b\u7883  d\u7885 a \u273 \u7871 n li\'ean t\u7909 c kh\'f3c \'f4m b\'e0i v\u7883  k\'eau t\'ean Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u d\u432 \u7899 i lo\u7841 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng \u273 \'f3 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7911  m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7859 ng l\u7869  l\'e0 v\'ec ch\u7883 u qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u kinh h\'e3i hao t\u7893 n qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u tinh l\u7921 c th\u7875  l\u7921 c, th\'e2n th\u7875  v\u432 \u7907 t qu\'e1 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng v\u7853 n h\'e0nh, v\'ec v\u7853 y l\'e2m v\'e0o tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i t\u7921  b\u7843 o v\u7879  ng\u7911  say?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, \u273 \u7875  t\u7841 m b\'e0i v\u7883  l\'ean \u273 \'f9i m\'ecnh, l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ra nh\'ecn, t\'e1m r\u432 \u7905 i s\'e1ng, t\'edn hi\u7879 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c, t\'ednh ra c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ng\u7911  th\u7901 i gian kh\'f4ng ng\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\'f3 n\u259 m cu\u7897 c g\u7885 i nh\u7905 , th\u7901 i gian kho\u7843 ng s\'e1u gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u h\'f4m qua, d\'e3y s\u7889  r\u7845 t quen thu\u7897 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7885 i l\u7841 i, l\'e0 l\'e3o b\u7843 n c\u7911 a nh\'e0 h\'e0ng c\u7853 u \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u7891  \u259 n nghe m\'e1y, n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t chi\u7873 u qua l\'fac \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7871 n cho c\u7853 u, nh\'e2n vi\'ean g\'f5 c\u7917 a nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai m\u7903 , h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 em c\u417 m \u273 \u7863 t \u7903  ph\'f2ng b\u7843 o an ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a ti\u7875 u khu c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e0 h\'e0ng \uc0\u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac s\'e1u gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u, nh\u432 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng h\u7873  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a, th\u7913  l\u7845 y v\'e0o l\'fac b\u7843 y gi\u7901  kia kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec r\u7891 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m c\u7911 a nh\'e0 h\'e0ng, li\'ean t\u7909 c n\'f3i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, xong li\u7873 n c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u r\u7901 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng k\'e9o t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  v\u7883  tr\'ed c\u361 , \'f4m b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi cung k\'ednh \u273 \u7863 t l\u7841 i l\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901 . Ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua th\u7913  kia cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ti\u7871 n v\'e0o, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 trong ba th\u7913 : c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  kh\'f4ng m\u7903 , b\'e0i v\u7883  tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  hay l\'e0 linh kh\'ed c\u7911 a linh ng\u7885 c c\'f2n th\u7915 a l\u7841 i \'edt \u7887 i, th\u7913  n\'e0o c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 ba th\u7913  h\u7907 p l\u7841 i c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch t\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  v\u7851 n nh\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7917 a trong c\u7917 a ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f3a r\u7845 t k\u7929 , nh\u432 ng t\'fai \u273 \u7891  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7891  c\'fang h\'f4m qua b\u7883  c\u7853 u b\u7887  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c g\u432 \u417 ng nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua, hai m\u7855 t c\u7853 u \u273 \u7887  ng\u7847 u, ho\'e0n to\'e0n s\u432 ng l\'ean, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n nh\'ecn th\u7845 y n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f2n cho l\'e0 c\u7853 u b\u7883  ch\'e0 \u273 \u7841 p hay b\u7883  ch\u7883 u th\u7853 t nhi\u7873 u u\u7845 t \u7913 c g\'ec \u273 \'f3. \u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin nh\u7855 n T\u7915  Giang g\u7917 i t\u7899 i, nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  c\u7853 u bu\u7893 i h\u7865 n h\'f4m nay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297  b\u7897  d\'e1ng c\u7853 u th\u7871  n\'e0y c\'f2n h\u7865 n h\'f2 c\'e1i g\'ec a, hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  tr\u7843 i qua chuy\u7879 n ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c x\'f3a b\u7887  nh\u7919 ng suy ngh\u297  t\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7865 p kia, ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n thanh t\'e2m qu\u7843  d\u7909 c th\'e0nh th\u7853 t l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i. Nh\u432 ng T\u7915  Giang \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t v\'ec c\u7853 u m\'e0 s\u7855 p x\u7871 p l\u7847 n n\'e0y, n\u7871 u b\'e2y gi\u7901  n\'f3i kh\'f4ng \u273 i th\'ec qu\'e1 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  m\u7863 t m\u361 i cho b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u. Ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, c\u7853 u v\u7897 i v\'e0ng l\u7845 y m\u7845 y vi\'ean \u273 \'e1 t\u7915  trong t\u7911  l\u7841 nh ra b\u7885 c v\'e0o kh\u259 n ch\u432 \u7901 m l\'ean m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u273 \u7875  tr\'e1nh cho T\u7915  Giang \u7903  tr\'ean b\'e0n c\u417 m l\'e0m m\u7889 i d\u7851 n \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f4i b\'ean l\'fang t\'fang, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a ch\u432 \u7901 m m\u7855 t v\u7915 a g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'e1o tr\u432 \u7899 c cho h\u7855 n, l\u7855 p b\u7855 p b\'e0y t\u7887  b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd t\u7913  kia n\u7919 a, v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7889 ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh r\u7845 t t\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u7903  trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i n\'f3i: "C\u7909 c t\u7849 y \'e0, t\u7899  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7899  kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p k\u7871 t h\'f4n."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng: "C\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  La Th\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng? Ti\u7875 u t\u7917  kia h\u7891 i c\u7845 p ba m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u n\'f3i b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng h\u7907 p v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n k\u7871 t h\'f4n, sau n\'e0y ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n t\u7921  do t\u7921  t\u7841 i s\u7889 ng \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i, b\'e2y gi\u7901  h\'e0i t\u7917  nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 hai tu\u7893 i r\u432 \u7905 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c ngh\u7865 n ra m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "... ch\'f3 kh\'f4ng s\u7911 a th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7855 n ng\u432 \u7901 i." Nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  ch\u7881  n\'f3i m\'e0 kh\'f4ng luy\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 k\u7929  n\u259 ng gi\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao l\'e0 b\uc0\u7857 ng h\u7919 u nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m, T\u7915  Giang \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i t\'ednh c\'e1ch Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i hi\'ea\u777 u r\'f5, bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u c\'f3 v\'e0i ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i "Qu\'e1i d\u7883 ", h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 ch\u7883 u \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng t\u7915  ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0 trong nh\'e0, tu\u7893 i c\'f2n tr\u7867  m\'e0 r\u7845 t m\'ea t\'edn c\u7893  h\u7911 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec l\'e0m s\u7869  r\u7845 t th\'edch \u273 i \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n ch\'f9a mi\u7871 u c\'e1c loa\u803 i c\u7847 u th\u7847 n b\'e1i Ph\u7853 t, mang \u273 \u7871 n cho h\u7855 n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 n\u7871 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 t s\u7921  xu\u7845 t gia, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y qu\'e1 k\u7923  qu\'e1i. Cho n\'ean m\u7863 c d\'f9 c\'f3 ch\'fat t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, nh\u432 ng T\u7915  Giang v\u7851 n r\u7845 t t\'f4n tr\u7885 ng \'fd mu\u7889 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang ch\u7885 c c\u432 \u7901 i, m\u7897 t b\u7919 a c\u417 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i, h\u7847 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng n\'f3i l\u7901 i n\'e0o, c\u361 ng li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t tr\'f4i qua, ngay c\u7843  ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c li\'ean l\u7841 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng trao \u273 \u7893 i v\u7899 i nhau. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 c\'f9ng c\u7843 m t\u7841  T\u7915  Giang hi\u7875 u cho m\'ecnh, \u259 n xong li\u7873 n \u273 \u432 a ba ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i t\u7921  m\'ecnh quay tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7841 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t n\u7917 a th\'ec g\u7863 p \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7887  d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, trong ng\u7921 c \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat run run. B\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 hai r\u432 \u7905 i chi\u7873 u, th\u7901 i gian c\'f2n s\u7899 m, bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng l\'fac \u7903  nh\'e0 tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, nh\u432 ng ai m\'e0 \u273 o\'e1n tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c sau khi m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i l\u7863 n, li\u7879 u th\u7913  ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua kia c\'f3 t\u7899 i g\'f5 c\u7917 a n\u7919 a hay kh\'f4ng? Ai bi\u7871 t n\'f3 c\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 m\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t \u273 \u7871 n m\'ecnh r\u7891 i hay kh\'f4ng? \u272 \'eam qua m\u7863 c d\'f9 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ngh\u297 a l\'e0 h\'f4m nay v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7897  nh\u7905  h\'f4m nay th\u7913  kia c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7903  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\u7853 u g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c l\'e1i xe v\u7873  ph\'eda nh\'e0 m\'ecnh n\u7919 a, run run r\u7849 y r\u7849 y m\'e0 d\u7915 ng xe v\'e0o ven \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho T\u7915  Giang.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang v\u7915 a ti\u7871 p \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i li\u7873 n h\u7887 i c\u7853 u: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 ? Sao th\u7871 ? Th\u7845 y s\u432  mu\u7897 i c\u7911 a t\u7899  xinh \u273 \u7865 p \u273 \u7893 i \'fd r\u7891 i h\u7843 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7893 i \'fd c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u. C\u7843  ng\'e0y nay c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n t\u7889 i qua, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fa \'fd hai c\'f4 b\'e9 kia h\'ecnh d\u7841 ng m\'f4 t\'ea ra sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i: "L\'e3o T\uc0\u7915 , b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u h\'f4m nay c\'f3 quay v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 kh\'f4ng? T\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n k\'ed t\'fac c\u7853 u \u7903  nh\u7901  m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?" K\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7885 c ti\u7871 n s\u297  l\'e0 ph\'f2ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a T\u7915  Giang \u273 \'e3 k\u234 \u769 t h\'f4n, c\'f2n thu\'ea nh\'e0 \u7903  ngo\'e0i tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c, l\'e2u l\'e2u m\u7899 i quay v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac \u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u ta kh\'f4ng v\u7873  \u273 \'e2u, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i t\u7899  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, h\'f4m nay m\u7865  t\u7899  g\u7885 i t\u7899  v\u7873  nh\'e0, t\u7899  \u273 ang chu\u7849 n b\u7883  thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c \u273 \u7875  v\u7873  \u273 \'e2y. Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867  nh\'e0 c\u7853 u b\u7883  sao \'e0? N\u7871 u c\u7853 u c\u7847 n th\'ec t\u7899  ch\u7901  c\u7853 u \u7903  ph\'f2ng, t\u7899  n\'f3i v\u7899 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\u7853 u v\u7915 a v\u7863 n c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7911  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng t\u7899 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \u7871 n k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 c\u7911 a T\u7915  Giang th\'ec c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 nam sinh k\'edn m\u7897 t l\u7847 u \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, gi\u7919 a c\'e1c ph\'f2ng ch\u7881  c\'e1ch m\u7897 t b\u7913 c t\u432 \u7901 ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 nam sinh tu\u7893 i tr\u7867  s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng tr\'e0n tr\u7873 , c\'f3 l\u7869  an to\'e0n h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i c\u259 n nh\'e0 v\u7915 a b\u7883  th\u7913  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 g\'ec kia \u273 \u7871 n th\u259 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7847 n ch\u7915  n\u7919 a, l\u7845 y c\u7899  n\'f3i ph\'f2ng l\u7847 u tr\'ean b\u7883  r\u7881  n\u432 \u7899 c v\u7851 n ch\u432 a s\u7917 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nhanh ch\'f3ng l\'e1i xe v\u7873  nh\'e0 l\u7845 y \u273 \u7891  d\'f9ng h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y, suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\u7847 m lu\'f4n b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7849 n th\u7853 n d\'f9ng v\u7843 i qu\u7845 n k\u7929  c\u7845 t v\'e0o trong ba l\'f4. Sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u l\u7841 i l\'e1i xe v\u7873  \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c T\'f4 D\'e2n, t\'ecm T\u7915  Giang nh\u7853 n ch\'eca kh\'f3a ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, \u273 \u432 a T\u7915  Giang v\u7873  nh\'e0, kh\'e9o l\'e9o t\u7915  ch\u7889 i l\u7901 i m\u7901 i nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh c\u7911 a m\u7865  h\u7855 n m\u7901 i c\u7853 u \u7903  l\u7841 i \u259 n c\u417 m t\u7889 i, th\u7915 a d\u7883 p tr\u7901 i ch\u432 a bi\u7871 n \u273 en tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng T\u7915  Giang.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng T\uc0\u7915  Giang \u7903  l\u7847 u s\'e1u, c\u417  b\u7843 n ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh h\u7855 n \u7903 , b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n ch\u7881  g\u7917 i m\u7897 t \'edt s\'e1ch v\u7899 i m\u7845 y th\u7913  linh tinh \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng s\u7869  quay v\u7873  l\u7845 y v\'e0i th\u7913 . C\u361 ng l\'e0 k\u7871 t c\u7845 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng tr\'ean b\'e0n d\u432 \u7899 i, tr\'ean chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n \u273 \u7875  m\u7897 t balo du l\u7883 ch v\'e0 hai t\'fai h\'e0nh l\'fd l\u7899 n, ngo\'e0i nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 ra th\'ec tr\u7889 ng tr\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n n\'ean T\u7915  Giang \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t qu\'e9t d\u7885 n ph\'f2ng, c\'f2n m\u7903  c\u7917 a s\u7893  th\'f4ng gi\'f3. Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi v\'e0o ph\'f2ng li\u7873 n \u273 em t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\u7917 a ch\'ednh c\u7917 a s\u7893  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f3a l\u7841 i, b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'ec c\u226 \u768 m \u273 i\'ea\u803 n thoa\u803 i ch\u417 i tr\'f2 ch\u417 i, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  th\'ec c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng sinh vi\'ean \u273 i \u273 \'e1nh r\u259 ng r\u7917 a m\u7863 t chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i h\'e0nh lang v\uc0\u7851 n th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n v\'e0 ti\u7871 ng \u273 \'f9a gi\u7905 n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a sinh vi\'ean, c\'f3 thanh \'e2m h\u417 i th\u7903  cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y an t\'e2m, c\u7853 u m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng, r\u7845 t nhanh li\u7873 n ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t qua bao l\'e2u, c\u7853 u m\u417  h\u7891  nghe th\u7845 y m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a theo nh\u7883 p, ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng kia kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i \u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c c\u7853 u t\u7915  trong gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\'ecn \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \'97\'97 m\u7897 t gi\u7901  s\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nhanh ch\'f3ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" \u273 ang g\'f5 c\u7917 a, ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a quen thu\u7897 c c\u7913 ng nh\u7855 c h\u7847 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ch\'fat thay \u273 \u7893 i kia khi\u7871 n cho c\u7853 u ngay l\u7853 p t\u7913 c t\u7881 nh t\'e1o l\u7841 i, \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng si\u7871 t th\'e0nh m\u7897 t \u273 o\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u432 \u417 n tay mu\u7889 n b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n, nh\u432 ng v\'f4 lu\u7853 n \u7845 n \u273 i \u7845 n l\u7841 i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Ch\u7895  T\u7915  Giang \u7903  l\'e0 k\'fd t\'fac cho ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7885 c ti\u7871 n s\u297 , nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 quy \u273 \u7883 nh bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  s\u7869  t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n c\u7855 t \u273 i\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, d\u7921 a v\'e0o \'e1nh s\'e1ng y\u7871 u \u7899 t kia g\u7855 t gao nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7917 a, tay ph\u7843 i l\u7841 i si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7921 ng tro c\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "K\'e9t.." m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\u7917 a \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean m\u7903  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e8n h\'e0nh lang \u273 \'e1ng l\u7869  ph\u7843 i s\'e1ng l\u7841 i m\u7897 t m\u7843 nh t\u7889 i t\u259 m, kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ch\'fat \'e1nh s\'e1ng n\'e0o, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u7903  n\u417 i s\'e2u trong \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong gi\'e2y l\'e1t b\uc0\u7883  d\u7885 a \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\'eau l\'ean, n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t sinh l\'fd l\u7853 p t\u7913 c d\'e1n \u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t, c\u7853 u h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng l\u7899 n th\u7903  g\u7845 p, kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n nh\'ecn xu\u7889 ng ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i. C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'fac n\'e0y n\'ean \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t hay l\'e0 n\'ean tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 g\'ec, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y n\'f3, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a, nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7917 a m\u7903  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'f5 r\'e0ng ph\'f2ng ng\uc0\u7911  b\u7889 n ph\'eda xung quanh \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7853 t c\u7913 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u k\'eau to l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng g\'e2y ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7917 a \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7853 u \u273 ang \u7903  trong m\u7897 t kh\'f4ng gian kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en \'f4n nhu \u273 em c\u7853 u \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, tay t\u7915  d\u432 \u7899 i v\u7841 t \'e1o c\u7853 u tham ti\u7871 n v\'e0o, nhu h\'f2a vu\u7889 t ve t\u7845 m l\u432 ng \u7849 m \u432 \u7899 t m\u7891  h\'f4i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, m\u7863 t d\'e1n t\u7899 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  h\'f4m qua h\'f4n l\'ean n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng ch\u7841 m l\'ean m\'f4i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i kia b\u7883  thu h\'fat d\u7851 n d\u7909  \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y m\'e0 h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\'f2n s\u7907  h\'e3i h\u417 n c\u7843  Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\'fat n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u417  h\u7891  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  kia d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n h\u7885 c d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng h\u7891 i l\'e2u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng l\'e0m ra h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngay sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 th\u7913  kia l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fat c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c nh\u7853 n bi\u7871 t y\u7871 u \u7899 t n\'e0y c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean to\'e0n b\u7897  d\u7921 a v\'e0o tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m qua li\'ean t\u7909 c b\u7883  r\'ecnh m\'f2 t\u7841 o th\'e0nh, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 ang nh\'ecn m\'ecnh ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang r\u7845 t s\u7841 ch s\u7869 . C\u7853 u th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 v\u432 \u417 n tay, \u7845 n c\'f4ng t\u7855 c b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Theo ti\uc0\u7871 ng vang c\u7911 a d\'f2ng \u273 i\u7879 n y\u7871 u \u7899 t, \u273 \'e8n ch\'e2n kh\'f4ng m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng nh\u7845 p nh\'e1y hai c\'e1i, s\'e1ng l\'ean, chi\u7871 u r\'f5 c\u259 n ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
