\cb3 C\'e1c d\'e3y k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 n\'e0y t\uc0\u7847 ng cao nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 t\u7847 ng b\u7843 y, nh\u432 ng t\u7847 ng b\u7843 y ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng kh\'f4ng gian kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\'e2y th\'e0nh b\u7889 n ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , cho n\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ban c\'f4ng l\u7847 u s\'e1u b\'ean n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng tr\'ean m\'e1i nh\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n \'97\'97 m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  m\'e9p m\'e1i nh\'e0, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n ti\u7871 n v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng, ph\'eda sau h\u7855 n m\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng c\'f2n c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7901  m\u7901  \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  tho\'e1ng th\u7845 y \'e1nh s\'e1ng h\u417 i y\u7871 u, h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 t\u7915  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ho\u7863 c \u273 \'e8n pin ph\'e1t ra. Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y h\u7859 n l\'e0 gi\u7843 ng vi\'ean v\'e0 c\'e1n b\u7897  ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i, nh\u432 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\'f9y ti\u7879 n ti\u7871 n l\'ean.\cb1 \
