\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915 ng nghe k\u7875  v\u7873  l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n t\'ecm k\u7867  ch\u7871 t thay.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7902  n\u417 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t oan s\u7869  sinh ra qu\u7927  ch\u7871 t oan, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia ng\'e0y qua ng\'e0y v\u7851 n lu\'f4n qu\u7849 n quanh t\u7841 i ch\u7895 , kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng t\'ecm ki\u7871 m k\u7867  ch\u7871 t thay, ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7887  tu\u7893 i, tinh th\u7847 n y\u7871 u, nh\u7845 t l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i trong \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915 ng c\'f3 \'fd ni\u7879 m t\'ecm \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1i ch\u7871 t l\u7841 i c\'e0ng d\u7877  b\u7883  ch\'fang qu\u7845 n l\'ean, tr\u7903  th\'e0nh "K\u7867  ch\u7871 t thay" .\cb1 \
