\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac \uc0\u7845 y m\u417  m\u417  h\u7891  h\u7891  kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u r\'f5, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  t\'e2m ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh m\u7897 t h\u7891 i, c\'f2n l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u7899  t\u7899 i l\u7901 i n\'f3i v\'e0 t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh trong tr\'ed nh\u7899  \u273 \'e3 \u7889  m\'e0u kia, c\'e0ng ngh\u297  trong l\'f2ng c\'e0ng b\u7845 t an, v\'f4 th\u7913 c \u273 \'e8 l\'ean b\'ecnh s\u7913  \u273 eo tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c c\'e1ch m\u7897 t l\u7899 p qu\u7847 n \'e1o. G\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\'ecm ph\u7843 i v\u7853 n r\u7911 i g\'ec, l\u7841 i li\'ean t\u7909 c g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, l\u7841 i bu\'f4ng b\'e0n tay \u273 ang b\'f3p ch\u259 \u803 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kia ra, h\'ecnh nh\u432  mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\u7871 t tuy r\u7857 ng nh\'ecn qua c\'f3 v\u7867  n\'f3 c\'f2n c\'e1ch m\'ecnh m\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7887 , nh\u432 ng th\u7913  kia v\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nhau, n\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  ngay l\u7853 p t\u7913 c xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7857 ng sau, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  lao t\u7899 i ph\'eda sau m\'ecnh b\'f3p ch\u259 \u803 t c\u7893  m\'ecnh \'e9p m\'ecnh nh\u7843 y l\u7847 u, m\'e0 b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
