\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y b\'ean c\uc0\u7841 nh truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng m\u7903  c\u7917 a, m\u7897 t thanh ni\'ean cao g\u7847 y \u273 eo k\'ednh \u273 en t\u7915  b\'ean ph\u7843 i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u273 i ra.\cb1 \
