\cb3 V\'ec chuy\uc0\u7879 n n\'e0y b\u7883  c\u7855 t ngang gi\u7919 a ch\u7915 ng, l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean ho\'e0n h\u7891 n l\u7841 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda t\u7847 ng cao nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n, m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\u7913  kia \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a, sinh vi\'ean \u273 \u7883 nh nh\u7843 y l\u7847 u kia gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t \'fd th\u7913 c ng\'e3 v\'e0o m\'e1i nh\'e0, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ph\'eda sau h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7891 ng lo\u7841 t x\'f4ng t\u7899 i khi\'eang h\u7855 n \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng ch\u7907 t l\u7841 nh. V\u7915 a r\u7891 i ch\u7881  l\'e0 ngh\u297  m\'e0 th\'f4i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i th\u7913  kia \u273 \'e3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  qu\u7845 n l\'ean m\'ecnh r\u7891 i ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u do d\u7921  \u273 \u432 a tay s\u7901  l\'ean c\u7893 , s\u7901  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0 da th\u7883 t b\u7883  gi\'f3 \u273 \'eam th\u7893 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh, l\'fac ma s\'e1t v\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay d\'e2ng l\'ean m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u7845 m \'e1p. Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn, sau l\u432 ng v\u7851 n l\'e0 ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  s\'e1ng \u273 \'e8n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec c\uc0\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7845 p th\u7887 m kh\'f4ng y\'ean b\u7845 t an nh\u432  c\u361 , nh\u432 ng m\'e0 th\u7913  kia \u273 \'fang l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i m\'ecnh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u b\u7883  qu\u7845 n l\'ean. \u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i hi\u7879 n th\u7901 i gian \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 r\u7841 ng s\'e1ng b\u7889 n gi\u7901 , ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7913 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a v\u7873 , r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 h\u7919 u kinh v\'f4 hi\u7875 m. Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7889 n t\u7909  t\u7853 p l\u7841 i c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  \u273 u\u7893 i t\u7843 n \u273 i, ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng \u7891 n \'e0o tan h\u7871 t, sau m\u7897 t h\u7891 i r\u7889 i ren, b\'f3ng t\u7889 i \u7903  b\'e3i \u273 \u7845 t tr\u7889 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c l\u7847 u m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c y\'ean l\u7863 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  g\u7885 i \u7903  l\u7841 i l\'e0m c\'f4ng t\'e1c gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t h\u7853 u qu\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quy\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh tr\u7903  v\u7873 tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7911  ti\u7871 p m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n, \u273 \u7913 ng d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng suy ngh\u105 \u771  m\'f4\u803 t ch\'fat, c\u7847 m l\u7845 y b\'e0i v\u7883  m\'e0u \u273 en v\u7889 n \u273 \u7863 t \u7903  tr\'ean b\'e0n h\u7885 c \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \'f4m r\u7891 i b\'f2 l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng k\'e9o v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, k\'e9o ch\u259 n nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y v\u7853 y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u \u273 \'e3 ch\'ecm v\'e0o gi\u7845 c ng\u7911  say, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7897 ng th\u7845 y kinh h\'e3i qu\u7927  d\u7883  g\'ec. Trong ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t ch\u7907 t c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7857 m c\u7841 nh \'f4m l\u7845 y m\'ecnh, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  th\'e2n h\'ecnh cao l\u7899 n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i m\u417  h\u7891 , d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7875  ho\'e0n to\'e0n \'f4m m\'ecnh v\'e0o trong l\'f2ng, \u7845 m \'e1p gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7847 n th\u7911  h\u7897 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y an t\'e2m, tr\u7903  m\'ecnh quay l\u7841 i \'f4m l\u7845 y b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng t\u7891 n t\u7841 i kia, kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng d\'e2ng l\'ean m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 l\'e2u kh\'f4ng c\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng m\u7897 ng, l\'fac t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh \u273 ang \'f4m ch\u259 n. L\u7847 n n\'e0y tuy r\u7857 ng ch\u7881  ng\u7911  ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n ba gi\u7901 , th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i b\u7893  sung tr\u7903  v\u7873  kh\'f4ng \'edt tinh l\u7921 c, c\u7853 u \'f4m b\'e0i v\u7883  v\u7899 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'f2 xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, sau khi thu d\u7885 n ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , \u273 \'e1nh r\u259 ng r\u7917 a m\u7863 t xong th\'ec gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'fac \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua, \u273 eo t\'fai x\'e1ch r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, \u273 em ch\'eca kho\'e1 ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7863 t \u7903  ph\'f2ng b\u7843 o v\u7879  d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u r\u7891 i r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y ch\uc0\u7881  m\u7899 i b\u7843 y gi\u7901  m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat s\'e1ng, tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7845 t t\u7889 i t\u259 m m\u7901  m\u7883 t, gi\u7901  l\'e0m vi\u7879 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u l\'fac t\'e1m gi\u7901 , l\'fac n\'e0y khu k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 v\u7851 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n y\'ean t\u297 nh, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai qua l\u7841 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i t\'ecm xe, tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \'f4m l\u7845 y \u7889 ng qu\u7847 n m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\u432 \u7903 ng l\'e0 m\'e8o hoang trong tr\u432 \u7901 ng ho\u7863 c l\'e0 b\u7883  c\'e0nh c\'e2y b\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7879 ch ra m\'f3c v\'e0o, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, c\'f2n mu\u7889 n c\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7875  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m r\'e1ch qu\u7847 n, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c qu\u7847 n n\'e0y th\'f4i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\u7901 i gian \u273 \u7875  v\u7873  nh\'e0 thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o r\u7891 i \u273 i l\'e0m n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f9y \'fd quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua, l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7855 t l\u7845 y qu\u7847 n c\u7853 u l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e1nh tay tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch d\'e0i th\'f2ng ph\u7911  k\'edn nh\u7919 ng v\u7871 t l\u7889 m \u273 \u7889 m c\u7911 a x\'e1c ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac r\uc0\u7841 ng s\'e1ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\'e1nh tay n\'e0y b\'f3p ch\u7863 t c\u7893  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \'e9p \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\u7843 y l\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7855 ng g\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \'e1nh b\u7841 o nh\'ecn xu\'f4i theo c\'e1nh tay kia, t\u7889 i h\'f4m qua th\u7913  kia b\'f2 r\u7841 p d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, v\u7851 n l\'e0 b\u7897  d\u7841 ng hai m\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 y t\u417  m\'e1u, ng\u361  quan c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 , so v\u7899 i t\u7889 i qua th\u7871  nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t \u273 i to\'e0n b\u7897  n\u7917 a ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7899 i, h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n ph\u7843 i tr\u7885 ng th\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0o \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7863 p m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 s\u7921  s\u7889 ng kia nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p \'e1c \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t minh b\u7841 ch th\u7913  n\'e0y l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u259 n c\u7843  ng\'e3 v\u7873  kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t m\'ecnh, h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t m\'ecnh r\u7891 i, n\'f3 s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7843 i tho\'e1t, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng v\u7899 i b\u7897  d\'e1ng n\'e0y c\u7911 a n\'f3, e r\u7857 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u7867  ch\u7871 t thay k\u7871  ti\u7871 p. L\'fac c\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7887  v\u7883  \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng kia c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i, th\u7875  ch\u7845 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u r\u7845 t d\u7877  b\u7883  b\u7855 t l\'e0m k\u7867  ch\u7871 t thay, c\u361 ng r\u7845 t d\u7877  b\u7883  h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u417 i v\'e0o m\u7889 i nguy tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t s\u7869  b\u7897 c ph\'e1t n\u259 ng l\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7921 c l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7841 i th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c sinh t\u7917 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871  ng\u7921  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i lo\u7841 i ma qu\u7927  kh\'f4ng r\'f5 n\'e0y, run r\u7849 y c\u7855 n r\u259 ng gi\u7853 t b\'ecnh s\u7913  \u273 eo tr\'ean c\u7893  xu\u7889 ng, n\u7855 m trong l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay \u273 \'e1nh v\u7873  ph\'eda c\'e1nh tay \u273 ang b\u7855 t l\u7845 y \u7889 ng qu\u7847 n m\'ecnh kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ecnh s\uc0\u7913  c\'f2n ch\u432 a ti\u7871 p x\'fac \u273 \u7871 n, c\'e1nh tay kia \u273 \'e3 gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\u7845 y uy hi\u7871 p c\u7921 c l\u7899 n, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean bu\'f4ng ra th\u7889 i lui v\u7873  ph\'eda sau, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i to\'e0n th\'e2n th\u7913  kia c\u361 ng t\'faa ra kh\'f3i \u273 en.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\uc0\u7871 p t\u7909 c nh\'ecn c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u7903  l\'e2u n\u7919 a, n\u7855 m b\'ecnh s\u7913  c\u7845 p t\u7889 c ch\u7841 y lao ra kh\u7887 i con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\u7885 , ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i qua l\u7841 i m\u7899 i tr\'ec ho\'e3n m\u7897 t h\u417 i, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c xe c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, m\u7903  c\u7917 a ng\u7891 i v\'e0o gh\u7871  l\'e1i, c\u7853 u m\u7899 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7845 t h\u7871 t s\u7913 c l\u7921 c co qu\u7855 p \u7903  \u273 \'f3, tay run r\u7849 y m\u7903  ra, hai c\'e1nh tay th\u7917  m\u7845 y l\u7847 n, m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a \u273 eo l\u7841 i d\'e2y b\'ecnh an treo b\'ecnh s\u7913  l\'ean c\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'e9t b\'ecnh s\u7913  v\'e0o trong \'e1o, c\u7843 m th\u7909  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh, \u273 \u7841 i n\'e3o bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi \u273 \u7897  \u7845 m c\u7911 a b\'ecnh s\u7913  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a g\u7847 n b\u7857 ng nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  c\u417  th\u7875 , l\'fac \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n t\'ecm l\u7841 i \'fd th\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7849 m b\u7849 m trong l\'f2ng n\'f3i: "Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , \u273 a t\u7841  ng\'e0i l\u7841 i c\u7913 u t\'f4i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n x\u7843 y ra li\'ean ti\u7871 p c\u361 ng l\'e0m cho c\u7853 u x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh, tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  ng\u259 n ch\u7863 n nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \'e1c \'fd kia, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o cam \u273 oan nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t t\u7899 i c\u7853 u, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng t\u7841 i th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c nguy c\u7845 p, th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7913 u c\u7853 u m\u7897 t m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i sai v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n ch\'fang s\u7907  h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
