\
\cb3 Di ch\uc0\u7913 ng duy nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u7891  \u259 n ngo\'e0i n\u7919 a, t\u7847 n su\u7845 t n\u7845 u \u259 n \u7903  nh\'e0 t\u259 ng l\'ean r\'f5 r\'e0ng, t\u7847 n su\u7845 t t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\'e0m c\u417 m cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7921  nhi\'ean c\u361 ng t\u259 ng l\'ean theo.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u417 n v\u7883  ngh\u7881  t\u7871 t Nguy\'ean \u272 \'e1n, m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e1t hai th\'f9ng hoa qu\u7843  m\u7897 t th\'f9ng rau v\'e0 m\u7897 t bao l\u7899 n h\u7891  \u273 \'e0o r\u7915 ng. H\u7891  \u273 \'e0o r\u7915 ng l\'e0 h\u7841 t nh\u7887 , l\u7899 n ch\u7915 ng ng\'f3n c\'e1i, m\'f9i v\u7883  tuy ngon, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 r\u7845 t kh\'f3 b\'f3c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y \uc0\u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u417 m n\u432 \u7899 c xong, m\u7903  ti vi b\u7853 t \u273 \u7841 i m\u7897 t k\'eanh d\u7841  h\u7897 i m\u7915 ng n\u259 m m\u7899 i n\'e0o \u273 \'f3, m\u7897 t b\'ean h\u7871 t s\u7913 c chuy\'ean ch\'fa c\u7847 m k\'ecm chuy\'ean d\u7909 ng k\u7865 p h\u7891  \u273 \'e0o. K\u7929  thu\u7853 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u qu\'e1 k\'e9m, ra tay kh\'f4ng nh\u7865  kh\'f4ng n\u7863 ng, m\u7897 t nh\'e1t k\u7865 p xu\u7889 ng, n\u7871 u v\u7887  kh\'f4ng v\u7905  th\'ec l\u7841 i l\'e0 k\u7865 p n\'e1t v\u7909 n. C\u7853 u mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng ch\u7885 n ch\u7885 n l\u7921 a l\u7921 a b\'f3c ra \u259 n, h\u7841 t v\u7905  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n h\'ecnh d\'e1ng g\'ec th\'ec b\u7887  v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng, h\u7841 t th\u7853 t v\u7845 t v\u7843  m\u7899 i b\'f3c ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ho\'e0n ch\u7881 nh th\'ec l\u7921 a ra \u273 \u7875  l\'ean tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i an v\u7883  \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n c\u7853 u t\u7921  tay d\'e2ng nh\'e2n h\u7841 t \u273 \'e0o l\'ean, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  li\u7873 n nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng li\u7871 m \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay c\u7853 u; th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\u7853 u n\'e9m nh\'e2n h\u7841 t \u273 \'e0o v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng m\'ecnh, th\u7913  kia c\u361 ng \'e1p t\u7899 i g\u7847 n th\u7915 a c\u417  li\u7871 m \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nguy\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e1n lo\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m m\u7899 i n\'e0y, c\'f3 nh\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  v\u7873 , c\'f3 m\u7845 y \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p tu\u7893 i c\'f2n tr\u7867  nh\'e0 \u7903  v\'f9ng kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng th\u7875  quay v\u7873 , c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n gi\u7889 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7885 i c\u7853 u c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i \u259 n c\u417 m mu\u7897 n \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  c\u7853 u t\u7915  ch\u7889 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  d\'e1m v\u7873  nh\'e0 sau m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901  \u273 \'eam, hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  c\'e1c \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p mu\u7889 n bao bi\u7879 t th\u7921  \u7903  v\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i \'f4 c\'f9ng nhau vui ch\u417 i, nghe v\'e0o tai gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7889 i c\u7843 nh kh\'fac d\u7841 o \u273 \u7847 u phim kinh d\u7883 . C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 chim s\u7907  c\'e0nh cong, m\u7897 t th\'e1ng n\'e0y th\u7853 t v\u7845 t v\u7843  m\u7899 i t\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e2y gi\u7901 , s\u7907  l\u7841 i g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, v\u7915 a nghe th\u7845 y \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u7921 c l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 i c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh qua l\u7877  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng tr\'e1nh kh\u7887 i t\u7883 ch m\u7883 ch, ban ng\'e0y l\'fac \u273 i mua s\u7855 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean thu\u7853 n tay \'f4m m\u7897 t chai r\u432 \u7907 u vang, l\'fac \u259 n c\u417 m u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ly. B\'e2y gi\u7901  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh b\'f3c h\u7841 t \u273 \'e0o b\'f3c \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0m ch\'e1n, l\u7841 i sinh ra v\'e0i ph\u7847 n t\u7911 i th\'e2n kh\'f4ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7889  t\'ecnh g\'e2y s\u7921 , tr\'ean tivi ph\u7891 n hoa n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i di \u273 \u7897 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng b\'e1o tin nh\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n c\u7911 a m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fac m\u7915 ng n\u259 m m\u7899 i, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 quan h\u7879  v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'ecnh nh\uc0\u432  t\u7915  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 n c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 t\u7853 t x\u7845 u n\'e0y, m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng l\'e2u r\u7891 i, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7843 m th\u7845 y qu\'e1 c\'f4 \u273 \u7897 c t\u7883 ch m\u7883 ch s\u7869  kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7911 i th\'e2n. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 t\u7911 i th\'e2n l\'e0 t\u7911 i th\'e2n \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i ta bao dung cho vi\u7879 c m\'ecnh c\u7889  t\'ecnh g\'e2y s\u7921 , thu\u7903  nh\u7887  th\'ec c\'f2n c\'f3 \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n chi\u7871 c b\'f3ng, t\u7911 i th\'e2n c\'e1i g\'ec ch\u7913 ? Sau t\u7911 i th\'e2n l\u7841 i sinh ra b\u7921 c b\u7897 i v\'f4 bi\'ean, lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 d\'f9 l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ecm th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng l\u7845 y v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7875  xua tan lo\u7841 i \u273 a c\u7843 m \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7913 t kho\'e1t l\u7841 i l\u7845 y ly v\'e0 r\u432 \u7907 u vang ra, r\'f3t hai ly, m\u7897 t ly \u273 \u7863 t \u7903  tr\'ean b\'e0n, m\u7897 t ly n\'e2ng trong tay, kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , n\u259 m m\u7899 i vui v\u7867 . N\u259 m t\u7899 i k\'ednh xin ng\'e0i chi\u7871 u c\u7889  nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n." Sau \u273 \'f3 u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t h\u417 i c\u7841 n s\u7841 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'ecnh c\uc0\u361 ng th\u7853 t l\'e0, v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i \u273 \'f3n n\u259 m m\u7899 i c\'f9ng v\u7899 i m\u7897 t t\u7845 m b\'e0i v\u7883  m\u7897 t nh\'fam tro c\u7889 t. Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i, Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u432 u l\u7841 i, ch\u7881  l\'e0 tro c\u7889 t c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  m\'e0 th\'f4i, cung ph\u7909 ng b\'e0i v\u7883  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t t\u7915  t\'f4n k\'ednh v\'e0 t\u7841  \u417 n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 khu\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  con n\'edt th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean l\'e0m b\u7841 n v\u7899 i b\'fap b\'ea c\u7911 a m\'ecnh m\'e0 sinh ra c\u7843 m t\'ecnh, "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi" b\u7843 o v\u7879  c\u7853 u nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y g\u7847 n g\u361 i tin c\u7853 y h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7907 ng "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi".\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t b\'ean tr\u7843  l\u7901 i tin nh\u7855 n, so\u7841 n tin nh\u7855 n ch\'fac m\u7915 ng n\u259 m m\u7899 i, m\u7897 t b\'ean u\u7889 ng r\u432 \u7907 u, b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c \u273 \'e3 u\u7889 ng h\u417 n n\u7917 a chai. R\u432 \u7907 u kh\'f4ng ghi n\u7891 ng \u273 \u7897 , nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7917 u l\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, t\u7889 i h\'f4m nay l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i t\'e0 g\'ec, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \'fd th\u7913 c h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n, th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nghe sai khi\u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ch\u7889 ng b\'e0n \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u li\u7871 c \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891  qu\u7843  qu\'fdt, v\u7853 y m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean xoa xoa \uc0\u273 \u7847 u, t\u7855 t TV, \'e2m thanh \u7891 n \'e0o r\'fat \u273 i, c\u7843  ph\'f2ng nh\'e1y m\u7855 t r\u417 i v\'e0o trong y\'ean l\u7863 ng. C\u7853 u ch\u7889 ng t\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng v\u7879  sinh, r\u7917 a m\u7863 t qua loa xong li\u7873 n n\u7857 m v\u7853 t l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \'fd ni\u7879 m cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng trong \u273 \u7847 u tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac m\'ea man l\'e0 h\'f4m nay m\u7863 c k\u7879  c\'e1i g\'ec \u273 \u7871 n g\'f5 c\u7917 a c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd n\u7919 a. C\u7853 u bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7891 n ng\u7911  v\'e0 m\'ea man \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n l\'e0m Tr\'ec Di\'ean qu\'ean t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, \'e1nh s\'e1ng tr\u7855 ng t\u7915  khe c\u7917 a r\u7885 i v\'e0o, v\u7915 a v\u7863 n chi\u7871 u s\'e1ng n\u7917 a chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  trong ch\u259 n tho\u7843 i m\'e1i d\u7877  ch\u7883 u kh\u7869  c\u7885  c\u7885 , hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean ng\u7911  r\u7845 t m\'e3n nguy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
