\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng xu\uc0\u7845 t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\'e0i nh\u7865  v\'f4 c\'f9ng, nh\u432 ng r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, d\'f9 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7913  hai \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  cho l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngay sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e8n trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch ch\u7853 p ch\u7901 n hai c\'e1i, t\u7855 t h\u7859 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng v\u7897 i m\'e0 \u273 i v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , th\u7843 n nhi\'ean ng\u7891 i \u7903  b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \u432 a tay nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng m\u417 n tr\u7899 n khu\'f4n m\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang ng\u7911  say, l\u7841 i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, li\u7871 m h\'f4n g\'f2 m\'e1 Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7865  nh\'e0ng m\'e0 thong th\u7843 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \'e1c qu\u7927  h\u432 \u7903 ng d\u7909 ng th\u7883 nh y\u7871 n huy\u7871 t nh\u7909 c cung ph\u7909 ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7855 n" hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u7913  th\u7871  m\'e0 ng\u7911  m\'e3n nguy\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i nh\u432  m\u7885 i ng\'e0y n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh ch\u7911  nh\'e0, k\'e9o ch\u259 n l\'ean \u273 em m\'ecnh c\u361 ng ph\u7911  v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c man m\'e1t \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n k\'edch th\'edch Tr\'ec Di\'ean run l\'ean, c\u7853 u n\u7881  non m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng o\'e1n gi\u7853 n, l\'f4ng m\'e0y h\u417 i chau l\u7841 i, l\u7841 i b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u432 a tay vu\u7889 t l\'ean l\'f4ng m\'e0y h\u417 i nh\u259 n l\u7841 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, l\u7841 i \u7845 n l\'ean m\u7897 t n\u7909  h\'f4n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7853 m r\'e3i h\'f4n t\u7915  l\'f4ng m\'e0y, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n kh\'f4ng th\u7887 a m\'e3n, nh\u432  \u273 \u7897 ng s\'e2u kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1y kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o l\u7845 p \u273 \u7847 y, d\'f9 c\'f3 \u273 em ng\u432 \u7901 i g\u7855 t gao kh\'f3a v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c th\u7871  n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a u t\u297 nh m\'e0u \u273 en \u273 \'e8 d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng, \u273 \u7863 t \u7903  n\u417 i s\'e2u trong linh h\u7891 n, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n lan ra, thi\'eau \u273 \u7889 t to\'e0n th\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7873 u h\'f2a treo t\u432 \u7901 ng trong ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean "C\'e1ch" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng m\u7903  ra, t\u7921  \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 n h\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  x\u7889 c ch\u259 n tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'ean, n\u7857 m ph\u7911  l\'ean th\'e2n th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng \u7845 m \'e1p, \u273 \'f2i h\u7887 i v\'f4 \u273 \u7897 ...\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t m\u7879 t m\u7887 i, h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 ng\u7911  m\u417  c\u7843  \u273 \'eam, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  n\u7893 i \u273 \u7871 n c\'f9ng l\'e0 m\u417  c\'e1i g\'ec; tr\'ean th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u361 ng c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c h\u417 i h\u417 i \u273 au nh\u7913 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 v\u7853 n \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7843  bu\u7893 i \u7903  ph\'f2ng t\u7853 p th\u7875  thao. B\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 l\'fac gi\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i ng\u7911  kh\'f4ng ngon m\u7899 i b\u7883  th\u7871  n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ng\u7911  l\'e2u r\u7891 i, r\'f5 r\'e0ng r\u7845 t d\u7877  ch\u7883 u. C\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 em to\'e0n b\u7897  quy t\u7897 i cho vi\u7879 c say r\u432 \u7907 u, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 au \u273 \u7847 u c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i say r\u432 \u7907 u, ch\'fat r\u432 \u7907 u vang kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta say ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac g\uc0\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\'f4 t\'ecnh n\'f3i ra chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y v\u7899 i T\u7915  Giang, T\u7915  Giang tr\u7883 nh tr\u7885 ng nghi\'eam nghi\'eam t\'fac t\'fac n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t: "N\'f3i theo g\'f3c \u273 \u7897  khoa h\u7885 c, c\u7853 u th\u7871  n\'e0y g\u7885 i l\'e0 \u273 au th\u432 \u417 ng chuy\u7875 n d\u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u432 \u769 c g\u7847 n ch\u234 \u769 t, c\u7853 u th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng n\'ean th\u7843 o lu\u7853 n v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  sinh v\u7853 t h\u7885 c v\u7899 i m\u7897 t t\'ean nghi\'ean c\u7913 u x\'e3 h\u7897 i h\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng b\u7883  T\u7915  Giang ch\u7863 n h\u7885 ng m\u7897 t c\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng coi chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n to t\'e1t g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\'e1t hi\uc0\u7879 n ra b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 cu\u7889 i th\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\'ean h\'f3a \u273 \u417 n ti\u7873 n \u273 i\u7879 n \'97\'97 t\u7915  khi d\'f9ng m\'e1y s\u432 \u7903 i trong nh\'e0, c\u7853 u ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  d\'f9ng nhi\u7873 u \u273 i\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, tuy r\u7857 ng h\'f4m nay m\'e1y s\u432 \u7903 i kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t l\u7855 m, trong nh\'e0 h\u417 i l\u7841 nh, nh\u432 ng bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i \u273 \u7855 p ch\u259 n ng\u7911  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c ph\u7843 i m\u7903  \u273 i\u7873 u h\'f2a. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 s\u7889  \u273 i\u7879 n s\u7917  d\u7909 ng th\'e1ng n\'e0y so v\u7899 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u m\u7903  \u273 i\u7873 u h\'f2a m\u7895 i ng\'e0y l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 nghi ng\u7901  trong l\'f2ng, cho d\'f9 li\'ean t\u7909 c b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n d\'ednh d\'e1ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n ma qu\'e1i l\'e0m lo\u7841 n. M\'e3i cho \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'eam khuya sau khi vi\u7871 t l\'e1ch t\u7855 m r\u7917 a xong, m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  ng\u7911  \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c g\u432 \u417 ng c\u7841 o r\'e2u, n\'fat th\u7855 t \'e1o ng\u7911  kh\'f4ng bu\u7897 c c\u7849 n th\u7853 n, l\'fac c\u7853 u c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng li\u7873 n l\u7887 ng ra, t\u7915  ph\u7847 n c\u7893  \'e1o m\u7903  r\u7897 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y r\'f5 ch\u7895  g\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u v\'fa tr\'ean ng\u7921 c c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\u7871 t \u273 \u7887  gi\u7889 ng t\u7909  huy\u7871 t, c\'f9ng v\u7899 i, ba v\u7871 t m\'e0u xanh nh\u432  ng\'f3n tay l\u432 u l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'fac hoan \'e1i t\'ecnh t\u7921  kh\'f3 n\'e9n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 l\u432 u l\u7841 i d\u7845 u h\'f4n v\'e0 d\u7845 u tay.\cb1 \
