\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  sai. C\u7853 u nh\u7899  v\'f4 c\'f9ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng, trong k\'fd \u7913 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, n\u259 m m\u432 \u7901 i tu\u7893 i \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u b\u7883  "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" \u273 \u7849 y xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u, camera gi\'e1m s\'e1t kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\'f3 b\u7845 t c\u7913  ai b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i l\u7841 i th\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t d\u7845 u b\'e0n tay t\'edm b\u7847 m nh\u7887 , h\u7871 t s\u7913 c lo s\u7907  b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i c\'e1c n\u417 i c\u7847 u th\u7847 n b\'e1i Ph\u7853 t, th\u7881 nh cao nh\'e2n ch\u7881  c\'e1ch b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\'e0, nh\u432 ng l\'e0 sau khi c\u7853 u \u273 eo tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  r\u7891 i c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  r\'f5 r\'e0ng, b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  kia li\u7873 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mang tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u, l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c c\u7911 a T\u7915  Giang th\u7913  kia r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t ki\'eang k\u7883  c\'e1i n\'e0y, l\'e0 v\u7853 t g\'ec d\'e1m tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7911  ngay c\u7841 nh tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e2y?\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng nay b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\'ecnh ng\u7911  \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t say, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fat c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0o, nh\u432 ng khi t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7879 t m\u7887 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ng\u7891 i y\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, c\u7843  \u273 \'eam c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  ng\u7911 , c\u7889  g\u7855 ng l\u432 u l\u7841 i m\u7897 t tia \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u7875  c\u7843 m \u7913 ng \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh b\'ean c\u7841 nh, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i ch\u7881  l\'e0 th\u7847 n h\u7891 n n\'e1t th\u7847 n t\'ednh, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u7883  tr\u7841 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 ng\u7911  m\u7845 t, ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y nh\'ecn tr\'e1i nh\'ecn ph\u7843 i, b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\'ecnh \u273 \'edch x\'e1c th\'e0nh th\'e0nh th\u7853 t th\u7853 t ng\u7911  \u7903  trong ch\u259 n, ng\u7911  r\u7891 i tr\u7903  ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, m\u7897 t \'edt \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c thay \u273 \u7893 i v\u7883  tr\'ed \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m nay v\uc0\u7915 a \u273 \'fang Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7917 a m\u7863 t, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tho\'e1ng t\u7881 nh t\'e1o m\u7897 t \'edt, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tr\'ec ho\'e3n n\u7919 a, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p l\'e1i xe ch\u7841 y l\'ean n\'fai T\'e2y Thanh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng v\'e0 ti\u7875 u \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7879  c\u7911 a \'f4ng, h\u7887 i m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i quen m\u7863 t kh\'e1c \u7903  \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n, h\u7885  n\'f3i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 v\u7873  qu\'ea b\'ean kia r\u7891 i, sau n\'e0y t\'e1m ch\'edn ph\u7847 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t, \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n ch\'f9a mi\u7871 u xung quanh T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883  ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 th\u259 m qua, \u273 a ph\u7847 n \u273 \u7873 u g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i l\u7915 a \u273 \u7843 o b\u7883 p b\u7907 m, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh th\u7853 t s\u7921  r\u7845 t \'edt, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, l\u7841 i c\'e0ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng. M\'e0 Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i r\u7845 t c\'f3 \'fd t\u7913 , tuy r\u7857 ng c\u361 ng d\'f9ng di \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0 c\'e1c lo\u7841 i thi\u7871 t b\u7883  truy\u7873 n tin hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7841 i, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c li\'ean l\u7841 c. Theo nh\u432  l\u7901 i \'f4ng n\'f3i, l\u432 u l\u7841 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c li\'ean l\u7841 c ch\u7881  l\'e0 cho c\'f3 li\'ean h\u7879 , b\u7885 n h\u7885  lo\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng n\'ean sinh ra qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u li\'ean h\u7879  v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i trong th\u7871  t\u7909 c, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac duy\'ean ph\u7853 n \u273 \'e3 h\u7871 t, n\'ean c\u7855 t \u273 \u7913 t th\'ec d\u297  nhi\'ean c\u7855 t \u273 \u7913 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u361 ng \u273 \'fang l\'e0 n\'f3i \u273 \u7913 t li\u7873 n \u273 \u7913 t, c\u7853 u ngay c\u7843  c\u7847 u c\u7913 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  th\u7845 y c\u7853 u s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t, l\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u quen m\u7863 t, bi\u7871 t l\'e0 kh\'e1ch quen c\u7911 a \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n, li\u7873 n gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u cho c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "Ch\u7895  ch\'fang t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\u7883  L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng m\u7899 i t\u7899 i, danh ti\u7871 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , r\u7845 t th\'e0nh th\u7853 t, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 k\u7867  l\u7915 a g\u7841 t, n\u7871 u c\u7853 u c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  th\'ec \u273 \u7915 ng ng\u7841 i t\'ecm \'f4ng \u7845 y th\u7917  xem."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng t\'ecm th\u7845 y Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng, v\u7853 y \u273 \u7875  L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng xem th\u7917  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, nh\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  gi\'fap ch\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t v\u7883  trung ni\'ean cao g\u7847 y, nh\'ecn qua tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i h\u417 n Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c qu\u7843  th\u7853 t l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'edch c\'e1ch ch\'ednh tr\u7921 c, th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\u7885 t v\'e0o s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p h\u7887 i c\u7853 u: "C\u7853 u c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec?" T\u432  th\u7871  c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7843 nh s\'e1t x\u7917  \'e1n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\uc0\u297  ngh\u297 , tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , n\'f3i: "Th\'e1ng n\'e0y ti\u7873 n \u273 i\u7879 n nh\'e0 con t\u259 ng r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u." N\'f3i xong k\u7875  l\u7841 i t\u7881  m\u7881  v\u7873  vi\u7879 c ti\u7873 n \u273 i\u7879 n b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u7899 i n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e2n n\u7917 a, L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \'e3 "\u7914 m" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng c\u259 \u769 t \u273 \u432 \u769 t c\u7853 u: "Ti\u7873 n \u273 i\u7879 n c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  th\'ec c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i \u273 i t\'ecm c\'f4ng ty \u273 i\u7879 n ch\u7913 , sao l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm t\'f4i? Mau \u273 i t\'ecm c\'f4ng ty \u273 i\u7879 n \u273 i, ki\u7875 m tra xem v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  ch\u7895  n\'e0o, xem c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7897 m \u273 i\u7879 n nh\'e0 c\u7853 u hay kh\'f4ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7889 t ru\u7897 t, kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i ra chuy\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n d\u7845 u v\u7871 t kh\'f4ng r\'f5.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng d\'f9ng \'e1nh m\u7855 t kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Ti\u7875 u t\u7917  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "\u272 \u7897 c th\'e2n \u7841 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'f3i: "Tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u t\'f4i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p, \u273 \u7915 ng t\'ecm \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  t\'f4i, \u273 i b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n x\u7871 p h\'e0ng m\'e0 xem. \u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n c\u361 ng ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, vi\u7879 c n\'e0y l\'e0 do c\u7853 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng qu\'e1 \'e1p l\u7921 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n, cho n\'ean m\u7899 i v\'f4 th\u7913 c t\'ecm ki\u7871 m th\u432  gi\u7843 i trong m\u7897 ng. T\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'e0 nhanh ch\'f3ng t\'ecm \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe ra ng\uc0\u7909  \'fd c\u7911 a L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng, m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i \u273 \u7887  l\'ean, v\u7915 a th\u7865 n v\u7915 a g\u7845 p, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7871 t s\u7913 c kh\'f3 x\u7917 . \'d4ng \u7845 y n\'f3i v\u7853 y \'fd l\'e0 m\u7845 y d\u7845 u v\u7871 t kia \u273 \u7873 u do c\u7853 u t\u7921  v\'e2n v\'ea ra sao? V\u7883  \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'e0y sao c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7913 ? Ng\'e0i \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i x\'e2y d\u7921 ng c\u7843  ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a x\'e3 h\u7897 i v\u259 n minh khoa h\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? \u272 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng ng\'e0i th\u7871  n\'e0y s\u7869  r\u7845 t d\u7877  tu\u7897 t m\u7845 t con l\'e0m con thay \u273 \u7893 i, t\'ecm \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871  l\u7921 c t\'f4n gi\'e1o t\u432  b\u7843 n ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a ph\u432 \u417 ng T\'e2y \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng h\u7887 i kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i n\u7919 a, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\u7883  L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'e0y s\u7869  ch\u7859 ng \u273 \u432 a ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7901 i khuy\'ean \u273 \'e1ng tin c\u7853 y n\'e0o, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7875  ch\u7913 ng minh m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 nghi th\u7847 n nghi qu\u7927  r\u7895 i h\u417 i \u273 \u7871 n ki\u7871 m chuy\u7879 n, do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c v\u7851 n \'fap m\u7903  n\'f3i ra bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p tr\u432 \u7899 c kia: "... L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c con ng\u7851 u nhi\'ean bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p, l\u7845 y tro c\u7889 t m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i mang b\'ean m\'ecnh, l\u7841 i th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng b\'e0i v\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 trong nh\'e0, con l\'e0 s\u7907  bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p n\'e0y m\u7845 t c\'f4ng hi\u7879 u, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p n\'e0y v\u7851 n c\'f2n t\'e1c d\u7909 ng con s\u7869  kh\'f4ng s\u7907 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u mu\u7889 n xin v\u7883  L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'e0y ch\u7881  \u273 i\u7875 m ch\'fat xem c\'e1ch \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 h\u7919 u \'edch hay kh\'f4ng, \u7903  d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng n\'e0o s\u7869  m\u7845 t t\'e1c d\u7909 ng \u273 \u7875  chu\u7849 n b\u7883  s\u7861 n s\'e0ng. Ai ng\u7901  n\'f3i c\'f2n ch\u432 a d\u7913 t l\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7855 t ngang.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng cau m\'e0y ph\u7845 t tay n\'f3i: "Ai ch\u7881  cho c\u7853 u bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p t\'e0 t\'ednh nh\u432  v\u7853 y? Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i n\'f3i n\u7919 a, c\u7853 u mang theo tro c\u7889 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, \u7903  nh\'e0 l\u7841 i th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng b\'e0i v\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 , kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 m x\u7845 u sao? C\u7853 u ph\u7843 i nghe l\u7901 i n\'e0y c\u7911 a t\'f4i, mau \u273 em tro c\u7889 t kia tr\u7843  l\u7841 i, b\'e0i v\u7883  th\'ec th\u7881 nh ra ngo\'e0i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 n\u7917 a n\u259 m kh\'f4ng t\u7899 i n\'fai T\'e2y Thanh, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 i l\'fac n\'e0o, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y bao gi\u7901 , nh\u432 ng hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean v\u7883  L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng m\u7899 i t\u7899 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng h\u7873  bi\u7871 t Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u432 \u417 ng ph\'e1p c\u7911 a \'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau hai c\'e2u tr\uc0\u7843  l\u7901 i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i v\u7883  n\'e0y L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng, th\u7853 m ch\'ed sinh ra m\u7845 y ph\u7847 n b\u7883  m\u7841 o ph\u7841 m \u7845 m \u7913 c, trong l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i d\'e1n cho \'f4ng nh\'e3n m\'e1c "kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng tin c\u7853 y", l\u7841 i c\'e0ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \'f4ng k\'e9m xa Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nghe l\u7901 i \'f4ng n\'f3i m\'e0 b\u7887  \u273 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ph\'e1p c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng. Kh\u7887 i c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i n\'f3i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tro c\u7889 t Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  b\'ean m\'ecnh trong kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t bao nhi\'eau l\u7847 n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7845 y L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'e0y \u273 \'fang l\'e0 b\u7897  d\'e1ng d\u7889 t \u273 \u7863 c c\'e1n mai, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 \'e0nh th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng c\'e1o t\u7915  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac c\uc0\u7853 u c\'e1o t\u7915  L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng v\u7851 n t\u7853 n t\'ecnh khuy\'ean b\u7843 o khuy\'ean c\u7853 u: "C\u7853 u tu\u7893 i n\'e0y \u273 ang l\'e0 thanh ni\'ean, n\'ean h\u7885 c t\u7853 p tri th\u7913 c v\u259 n h\'f3a khoa h\u7885 c nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n, kh\'f4ng n\'ean c\'f2n tr\u7867  m\'e0 l\'e0m nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c phong ki\u7871 n m\'ea t\'edn kia."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ho\'e0i nghi L\uc0\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\'e0 \u273 \u7891 ng ch\'ed do v\u259 n ph\'f2ng huy\u7879 n n\'fai T\'e2y Thanh ph\'e1i \u273 i \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n tr\'ean n\'fai T\'e2y Thanh \u273 \u7875  x\'e2y d\u7921 ng c\'f4ng t\'e1c duy tr\'ec t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u l\u7901 i L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng n\'f3i ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 khuy\'ean gi\u7843 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng \'edt, chuy\u7879 n ti\u7873 n \u273 i\u7879 n n\'e0y b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7853 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  theo h\u432 \u7899 ng k\u7923  d\u7883  ma qu\'e1i n\u7919 a, khi n\'e0o c\'f3 qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7901  th\'ec m\u7899 i li\'ean h\u7879  t\u7899 i, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  ph\u7843 i \u273 i c\'f4ng ty \u273 i\u7879 n tra m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  ph\u7847 n m\u7845 y d\u7845 u v\u7871 t kia... \u273 ang l\'e1i xe Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i h\u417 i \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t l\'ean, tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'ecnh s\u7869  c\'f3 s\u7903  th\'edch ng\u7911  r\u7891 i t\u7921  s\u7901  ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\'f3 khi th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 ch\'ednh m\'ecnh v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\'e0o n\u7863 n ra d\u7845 u v\u7871 t kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng? C\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  m\u7897 ng du m\'e0, ai bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c trong l\'fac ng\u7911  m\u417  b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7869  l\'e0m ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i qu\u7843  th\u7921 c ch\u7881  l\'e0 nghi th\u7847 n nghi qu\u7927 , c\'f2n h\u417 n l\'e0 b\u7883  l\u7915 a, L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng ngay th\u7859 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 th\u7875  khuy\'ean nh\u7911  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'edch l\u117 \u771 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c danh ti\u7871 ng t\u7889 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'f3 hi\u7875 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng lu\'f4n tin t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u417 ng lai s\u7869  t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p h\u417 n, gi\u7901  \u273 \'e2y Tr\'ec Di\'ean coi tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432  c\'e2y c\u7887  c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tin c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec d\'e1m \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7911  tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u th\'e1i tu\u7871 , c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p l\u432 u l\u7841 i d\u7845 u v\u7871 t tr\'ean ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh. \u272 em so s\'e1nh v\u7899 i m\u7845 y c\'e1ch gi\u7843 i th\'edch "Ch\'ednh m\'ecnh th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng v\'f4 th\u7913 c ni\u7871 t ra" "Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ni\u7871 t l\'fac n\'e0o m\'e0 ra" ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i d\u7877  ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 c d\'f9 v\u7853 y, sau khi v\u7873  nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lo l\u7855 ng th\u7845 p th\u7887 m m\u7845 y ng\'e0y, th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi c\u7843 m gi\'e1c x\'e1c th\u7921 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng g\'ec kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7899 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n th\u7843  l\u7887 ng trong l\'f2ng. M\u7895 i ng\'e0y sau khi ng\u7911  d\u7853 y th\'e2n th\u7875  kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean kh\'f4ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'edch \u7913 ng hay l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7871 t \'e2m l\u7883 ch c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c \u7903  \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  nhi\u7873 u, m\u7879 t nh\u7885 c n\'ean m\u7899 i b\u7883  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, m\u7845 y ng\'e0y tho\'e1ng ch\'fat thanh nh\'e0n n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7889 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t nhanh Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c d\u7901 i \u273 i l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd \'97\'97 \u273 \'e3 b\u432 \u7899 c sang n\u259 m m\u7899 i, ch\'fa c\u7853 u g\u7885 i c\u7853 u quay v\u7873  Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  \u259 n t\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng ch\'fa l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n duy nh\u7845 t hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao ch\'fa c\u361 ng c\'f3 nh\'e0 c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7853 u qua \u273 \'f3 c\'f9ng l\u7855 m c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t th\'e2n th\'edch, nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n th\'ec v\u7851 n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i, n\u7871 u giao th\u7915 a m\'f9ng m\u7897 t c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\u7899 i, m\u7907  c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  l\'fang t\'fang. H\u417 n n\u7919 a m\u7907  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m l\u7897  ra \'fd t\u7913  mu\u7889 n gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u v\u7899 i c\u7853 u v\u7899 i ch\'e1u g\'e1i m\'ecnh, l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u7853 u t\u7899 i kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng, ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n k\u7871 t th\'e2n n\'e0y, b\u7843 n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y v\u7915 a kh\'f3 x\u7917  v\u7915 a nh\u7913 c \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\u7877  m\u7915 ng n\u259 m m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng quay v\u7873 , d\'f9 sao \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i sau c\'f9ng v\u7851 n \u7903  \u273 \'f3, b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'f4ng b\'e0 nu\'f4i l\u7899 n, ng\'e0y t\u7871 t \u273 i t\u7843 o m\u7897  cho cha m\u7865  kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 i t\u7871  b\'e1i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u7841  quy\u7871 t t\'e2m \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m s\u7869  qua nh\'e0 ch\'fa, \u7903  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ng\'e0y r\u7891 i \u273 i ngay, n\'f3i \u7903  \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  ph\u7843 i \u273 i l\'e0m, c\'f3 l\u7869  ch\'fa m\u7907  c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng l\u432 u l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  r\'f5 ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c cu\u7889 i m\u7895 i n\u259 m b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng e d\'e8 mua s\u7855 m m\u7897 t phen, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh mu\u7889 n \u273 em c\u7843  nh\'e0 t\'e2n trang ho\'e0n to\'e0n, trang tr\'ed \u273 \u7847 y kh\'f4ng kh\'ed n\u259 m m\u7899 i, c\u361 ng g\u7885 i c\u7843  nh\'e0 ch\'fa v\u7873  \u259 n b\u7919 a c\u417 m \u273 o\'e0n vi\'ean. Nh\u7919 ng k\'fd \u7913 c n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\'f3 \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n c\u7853 u, tuy r\u7857 ng hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  trong nh\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u lo li\u7879 u nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c n\'ean lo li\u7879 u, c\'e2u \u273 \u7889 i T\u7871 t ch\u7919  Ph\'fac \u273 \'e8n m\'e0u \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng thi\u7871 u.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c kia b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i c\'f3 th\'f3i quen ng\'e0y ba m\u432 \u417 i T\u7871 t d\'e1n ch\u7919  Ph\'fac, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng k\u7871  t\u7909 c \u273 i\u7875 m \u7845 y, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u d\u7885 n d\u7865 p nh\'e0 c\u7917 a qu\'e9t s\u7841 ch m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, b\u7853 t m\'e1y lau nh\'e0, \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u297 a nh\u7887  t\u7921  m\'ecnh ch\u7841 y lo\u7841 n tr\'ean s\'e0n nh\'e0 lau ch\'f9i, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac b\u7897  n\u7841 p \u273 i\u7879 n c\u7911 a n\'f3 g\u7847 n h\u7871 t \u273 i\u7879 n, n\'f3 c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  m\'ecnh ch\u7841 y \u273 i ti\u7871 p m\'e1y s\u7841 c \u273 i\u7879 n \u273 \u7875  n\u7841 p \u273 i\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean x\'e1ch m\uc0\u7897 t t\'fai c\'e2u \u273 \u7889 i T\u7871 t ch\u7919  Ph\'fac v\'e0 b\u259 ng d\'ednh hai m\u7863 t, ch\u7863 n l\u7841 i c\u7917 a, b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'ec \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i d\'e1n ch\u7919 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Truy\uc0\u7873 n th\u7889 ng trong n\u432 \u7899 c l\'e0 c\'e2u \u273 \u7889 i T\u7871 t ch\u7919  Ph\'fac c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'f3n ph\'fac kh\'ed xua x\'fai qu\u7849 y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a ng\'e2m nga h\'e1t v\u7915 a d\'e1n v\u7915 a ngh\u297 , ch\u7881  hy v\u7885 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  th\u7871 , \u273 em t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i ng\u259 n \u7903  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n l\'fac d\'e1n xong c\u7853 u lui ra sau m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c nh\'ecn k\u7929  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, t\u7921  th\u7845 y \u273 \'e3 c\'e2n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u7859 ng phiu, v\'ec v\u7853 y h\'e0i l\'f2ng \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  quay \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi c\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i \u273 i v\'e0o nh\'e0, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n gi\'f3 t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u th\u7893 i t\u7899 i, l\u7841 i tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p \u273 em ch\u7919  Ph\'fac m\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a d\'e1n xong th\u7893 i l\'ean m\u7897 t g\'f3c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn k\u7929  s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e0 c\'f3 tang s\uc0\u7921  ch\u432 a \u273 \u7847 y k\u7923  th\'ec ch\'fa \'fd kh\'f4ng n\'ean d\'e1n ch\u7919  Ph\'fac treo c\'e2u \u273 \u7889 i T\u7871 t, ch\u7913  \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3i l\'e0 nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903 , m\'e0 tang k\u7923  c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  v\u7851 n c\'f2n ch\u432 a qua.\cb1 \
