\cb3 Em h\uc0\u7885  \u272 \u7895  \u272 \'ecnh \u272 \'ecnh \u7903  n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i \u273 \'e3 l\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y \u273 ang \u273 i h\u7885 c, trong nh\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fa v\'e0 m\u7907 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7875  qu\'e0 xu\u7889 ng, ng\u7891 i kh\'f4ng l\'e2u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  \u259 n tr\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7907  Ho\'e0ng Th\u7909 c c\u432 \u7901 i x\'e3 giao n\'f3i: "\u272 i th\'f4i, \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i \u259 n c\u417 m, ch\'fa con \u273 \u7863 t b\'e0n \u7903  *nh\'e0 h\'e0ng t\u432  gia g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y r\u7891 i."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (nh\'e0 h\'e0ng t\uc0\u432  gia: \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 s\u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng do ch\u7911  nh\'e0 h\'e0ng l\'e0m, b\'ean ngo\'e0i nh\'e0 h\'e0ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 bi\u7875 n hi\u7879 u, kh\'f4ng c\u7889  \u273 \u7883 nh menu, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nh\'e2n vi\'ean ph\u7909 c v\u7909 , nh\u432 ng bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p ch\u7871  bi\u7871 n th\u7913 c \u259 n th\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0 gia truy\u7873 n, c\'f3 h\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, h\u417 n n\u7919 a s\u7889  l\u432 \u7907 ng cung \u7913 ng c\'f3 h\u7841 n)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7913 t l\u7901 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\u7899  ra vi\u7879 c g\'ec n\'f3i: "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, c\u7843  nh\'e0 anh trai m\u7907  l\'e1t n\u7919 a c\u361 ng t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, ch\'e1u g\'e1i Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n c\u7911 a m\u7907  v\u7899 i con tu\u7893 i kh\'f4ng ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch l\u7855 m, hai \u273 \u7913 a c\u361 ng n\'ean l\'e0m quen m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa \uc0\u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh nh\u7865  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, c\u7843  nh\'e0 con g\'e1i nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta T\u7871 t \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m kh\'f4ng \u7903  nh\'e0 l\u7841 i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, ai c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec. Ng\u432 \u7901 i ta "Nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh" nh\u432  th\u7871 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 h\'e0ng, kh\'f4ng l\'e2u sau m\u7897 t nh\'e0 anh trai Ho\'e0ng Th\u7909 c c\u361 ng \u273 \u7871 n. Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n dung m\u7841 o tuy kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 xinh \u273 \u7865 p, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng x\u7845 u, b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i, trang \u273 i\u7875 m ch\u432 ng di\u7879 n li\u7873 n l\u7897  ra n\'e9t thanh xu\'e2n m\u7929  l\u7879 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ch\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7855 t c\'f4 ch\'e1u g\'e1i n\'e0y c\u7911 a v\u7907 , m\u7897 t l\'e0 v\'ec b\u7843 n th\'e2n huynh tr\u432 \u7903 ng Ho\'e0ng Th\u7909 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'ed v\u432 \u417 n l\'ean, th\'edch kh\'f4ng l\'e0m m\'e0 h\u432 \u7903 ng, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\'f2n \u273 \'e1nh b\u7841 c, m\u7845 y n\u259 m nay m\u7863 c d\'f9 n\'f3i l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 cai, nh\u432 ng \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh v\u7851 n nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c th\u7847 m ph\'ea b\'ecnh h\u7855 n, ch\u7883  d\'e2u Ho\'e0ng Th\u7909 c l\u7841 i c\'f3 ph\u7847 n ham h\u432  vinh; hai l\'e0 Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n \u7903  trong lo\u7841 i gia \u273 \'ecnh n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ra kh\u7887 i b\'f9n m\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\'ednh b\'f9n, m\u7863 c d\'f9 kh\'f4ng g\'e2y ra v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  l\u7899 n nh\u432  c\u7901  b\u7841 c, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i h\u7885 c gi\u7889 ng cha m\u7865  kh\'f4ng n\u7895  l\u7921 c ph\u7845 n \u273 \u7845 u, vi\u7879 c h\u7885 c c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n qua loa cho xong, d\u7921 a v\'e0o ti\u7873 n trong nh\'e0 m\'e0 h\u7885 c l\'ean. Sau khi Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p, \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh v\'ec m\u7863 t m\u361 i c\u7911 a v\u7907 , gi\'fap c\'f4 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 c v\u7883  th\u432  k\'fd \u7903  trong m\u7897 t c\'f4ng ty quen, nh\u432 ng c\'f4 g\'e1i n\'e0y l\u7841 i v\u7915 a ng\u7841 i v\u7845 t v\u7843  v\u7915 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p ch\'e8n \'e9p, ch\u432 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y ng\'e0y \u273 \'e3 b\u7887  l\'e0m. V\u7873  sau nghe n\'f3i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7921  m\'ecnh t\'ecm vi\u7879 c, nh\u432 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh c\u361 ng l\u432 \u7901 i quan t\'e2m \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n nh\'e0 v\u7907 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i han n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'e2n r\u7845 t m\u7851 n c\'e1n, trong l\'f2ng h\u7855 n, ch\'e1u trai b\'ean ngo\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh t\u7915  nh\u7887  cha m\u7865  \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t, nh\u432 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng g\'e2y ra sai l\u7847 m g\'ec, h\u7885 c h\'e0nh c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7875  m\'ecnh s\u7855 p x\u7871 p thu\u7853 n thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i l\u7907 i m\'e0 l\'e0m, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\u7847 u qua ai kh\'e1c. Tuy r\u7857 ng v\u7899 i t\u432  c\'e1ch l\'e0 con trai th\'ec d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  h\u432 \u7899 ng n\u7897 i qu\'e1 m\u7913 c v\'e0 thi\u7871 u h\u7909 t m\u7841 nh d\u7841 n, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng l\'e0 \u273 \u7913 a tr\u7867  r\u7845 t ngoan. Ch\'ednh h\u7855 n c\'f2n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n kh\'f4ng t\u432 \u417 ng x\u7913 ng, nh\u432 ng m\u7897 t l\'e0 v\u7907  \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7873  c\u7853 p qua m\u7845 y l\u7847 n, kh\'f4ng ti\u7879 n b\u7887  qua m\u7863 t m\u361 i c\u7911 a v\u7907  l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, hai l\'e0 c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n d\'f9ng vi\u7879 c n\'e0y nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'ean c\'e2n nh\u259 \u769 c chuy\u7879 n chung th\'e2n \u273 \u7841 i s\u7921  r\u7891 i. H\u7855 n ngh\u297  g\u7863 p m\u7863 t m\u7897 t l\u7847 n th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u7871 t hy v\u7885 ng th\'ec coi nh\u432  xong, m\u7899 i t\'f9y \'fd \u273 \u7875  Ho\'e0ng Th\u7909 c s\u7855 p x\u7871 p l\u7847 n g\u7863 p m\u7863 t n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'e0 kh\u7855 c, m\u7863 c d\'f9 \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ki\u7875 u "K\u7871 t th\'e2n" n\'e0y r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng th\'edch nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n gi\u7919  b\u7897  d\u7841 ng \'f4n h\'f2a l\u7877  \u273 \u7897 ; b\'ean n\u7919  tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn c\u361 ng r\u7845 t d\u7883 u d\'e0ng ng\u432 \u7907 ng ng\'f9ng, Ho\'e0ng Th\u7909 c v\'e0 anh trai ch\u7883  d\'e2u m\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i l\u7841 i t\u7841 o b\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed s\'f4i n\u7893 i, m\u7897 t b\u7919 a c\u417 m tr\'f4i qua c\u361 ng coi nh\u432  h\'e0i h\'f2a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m c\'e1 h\u7845 p trong m\'e2m, m\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ho\'e0ng Th\uc0\u7909 c \u273 \u7909 ng c\'f4 m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? Kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n ng\uc0\u7849 ng m\u7863 t, \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n c\u7911 a *nh\'e3 gian m\'e0u tr\'e0 nh\u7841 t chi\u7871 u r\'f5 g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch c\'f9ng m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7899 n nh\u432  h\u7841 t \u273 \u7853 u c\u7911 a c\'f4. M\'f4i c\'f4 tho\'e1ng run run, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Ho\'e0ng Th\u7909 c: "C\'e1, c\'e1 chuy\u7875 n \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7855 t. . ."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (nh\'e3 gian: ph\'f2ng cao c\uc0\u7845 p)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Ho\'e0ng Th\uc0\u7909 c v\u7851 n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng: "L\'e0m sao? V\u7851 n ch\u432 a ch\'edn?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n d\uc0\u7889 c s\u7913 c li\u7873 u m\u7841 ng l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, t\u7921 a h\u7891  s\u7855 p kh\'f3c l\'ean, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean th\'e9t to: "N\'f3 \u273 ang nh\'ecn con! N\'f3 c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i con! Con th\u7845 y n\'f3 b\u7883  gi\u7871 t b\u7883  m\u7893  b\u7909 ng c\u7841 o v\u7843 y, trong b\u7909 ng n\'f3 c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t con c\'e1 con! C\'e1 con b\u7883  kho\'e9t ra, c\u361 ng \u273 ang c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i con! N\'f3 mu\u7889 n chui v\'e0o trong b\u7909 ng con!"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Khung c\uc0\u7843 nh v\u7889 n \u273 ang \u7845 m \'e1p b\u7903 i v\'ec ng\u7919  \u273 i\u7879 u qu\u7927  d\u7883  v\'e0 l\u7901 i n\'f3i c\u7911 a Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n m\'e0 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u tr\u7903  n\'ean \'e2m l\'e3nh, Ho\'e0ng Th\u7909 c nghe xong c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, trong l\'f2ng ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh, s\u7907  run c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7865  c\u7911 a Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u432  ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 i\u7873 u g\'ec, bi\u7871 n s\u7855 c, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng che k\'edn mi\u7879 ng con g\'e1i, m\u7855 ng: "Con l\'e0m sao th\u7871 ? Ban ng\'e0y g\u7863 p qu\u7927  hay sao! N\'f3i b\u7853 y b\u7841  g\'ec \u273 \'f3!"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n b\uc0\u7883  m\u7865  che mi\u7879 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e2m thanh n\'e0o n\u7919 a, nh\u432 ng trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng l\u7841 i ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng "H\'e0 h\'e0", gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ti\u7871 ng kh\'f3c qu\u7927  d\u7883  n\'e0o \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e2n v\uc0\u7853 t ch\'ednh \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y, b\u7919 a c\u417 m n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng \u259 n ti\u7871 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, m\u7865  Ho\'e0ng \'e1y n\'e1y c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng c\'f9ng ch\u7891 ng mang con g\'e1i r\u7901 i \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\u432 ng m\'ecnh ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh t\u7915 ng tr\u7853 n, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\'fang t\'e0, m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i l\'e0 l\u7895 i \u7843 o gi\'e1c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u hay kh\'f4ng, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'fac \u7845 y Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n c\'f2n mu\u7889 n n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3, l\u7841 i b\u7883  m\u7865  m\'ecnh k\u7883 p th\u7901 i ng\u259 n l\u7841 i. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\u7853 u \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c k\u7871 t duy\'ean n\'e0y v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n, c\u361 ng t\u7921  nh\u7853 n m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh, ch\u7881  l\u7877  \u273 \u7897  bi\u7875 u \u273 \u7841 t quan t\'e2m, c\u361 ng th\'e0nh t\'e2m th\'e0nh \'fd \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  m\u7907  n\'ean \u273 \u432 a ch\'e1u g\'e1i m\'ecnh \u273 i ch\'f9a Th\'e1i An \u7903  ngo\u7841 i \'f4 th\'e0nh ph\u7889  xem th\u7917  xem c\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i c\'e1i g\'ec hay kh\'f4ng, xong c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh nghe \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t c\'e2u "ch\'f9a Th\'e1i An" kia c\u361 ng nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u7915 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'e1u trai b\'ean ngo\uc0\u7841 i n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\'ea t\'edn. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u \u273 i\u7875 m \u7845 y h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\u7841 i l\'e0 h\u7885 c t\u7915  m\u7865  m\'ecnh, h\u7855 n lu\'f4n lu\'f4n k\'ednh y\'eau m\u7865  h\u7855 n, t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7899 i nay c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ti\u7879 n n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7843 i qua s\u7921  ki\u7879 n n\'e0y, chuy\u7879 n t\'e1c h\u7907 p hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a. V\u7873  sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe n\'f3i v\u7915 a qua ng\'e0y m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m Ho\'e0ng Ph\'e2n Ph\'e2n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'ednh h\'f4n v\u7899 i m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c. C\u7853 u n\'f3i th\u7847 m trong l\'f2ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\u7907  \u273 \'e3 b\u7843 o con g\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i ta \u273 i ch\'f9a Th\'e1i An xem qua ch\u432 a, b\u7857 ng kinh nghi\u7879 m th\u7921 c t\u7871  t\u7915 ng tr\u7843 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, xung quanh Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883 , ch\'f9a Th\'e1i An l\'e0 n\u417 i \u273 \'e1ng tin nh\u7845 t. L\u7869  n\'e0o sau khi xem xong, \u273 \u7841 i s\u432  trong ch\'f9a n\'f3i \u273 \'fang l\'e0 \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3, \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  mau ch\'f3ng k\u7871 t h\'f4n *xung h\u7881  n\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \'ednh h\'f4n nhanh nh\u432  v\u7853 y?\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (xung h\uc0\u7881 : l\'e0m vi\u7879 c h\u7881 , nh\u432  c\u432 \u7899 i con d\'e2u \u273 \u7875  gi\u7843 i tr\u7915  v\u7853 n xui, t\'e0 kh\'ed)
