\cb3 M\'ecnh c\'f3 n\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng th\u7915 a d\u7883 p n\u259 m m\u7899 i k\u7871 t h\'f4n xung h\u7881  \u273 \u7875  tr\u7915  t\'e0 kh\'f4ng nh\u7881 ? \'dd ngh\u297  n\'e0y ch\u7881  chuy\u7875 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c qu\u259 ng ra sau \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec xu\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n, hay v\'ec qua n\u259 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i th\'eam m\u7897 t tu\u7893 i, t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u cho r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n tu\u7893 i d\u7921 ng v\u7907  g\u7843  ch\u7891 ng, b\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng th\'ec s\u7869  gi\'e0 m\u7845 t, hay l\'e0 \u273 \u417 n thu\u7847 n ch\u7881  v\'ec \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m m\u7899 i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i r\u7843 nh r\u7895 i, ng\u432 \u7901 i quen mu\u7889 n gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n nh\u7899  r\'f5 l\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 T\u7915  Giang mu\u7889 n gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u s\u432  mu\u7897 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, b\u7843 n th\'e2n li\u7873 n li\'ean ti\u7871 p g\u7863 p qu\u7927 , m\u7907  mu\u7889 n gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u ch\'e1u g\'e1i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng sao, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng b\u7883  nghi l\'e0 tr\'fang t\'e0, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 \u273 \u7871 n c\'f9ng l\'e0 c\'f3 li\'ean quan t\u7899 i c\u7853 u hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i th\uc0\u7875  ch\u7845 t n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p gieo tai h\u7885 a cho ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\uc0\u7887 i c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i n\'f3i, gi\u7843  s\u7917  c\u7853 u v\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'f4 g\'e1i y\'eau nhau, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u7903  trong r\u7841 p chi\u7871 u phim hay qu\'e1n c\'e0 ph\'ea nhu t\'ecnh m\u7853 t \'fd ch\'e0ng ch\'e0ng thi\u7871 p thi\u7871 p, nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u273 eo m\u7897 t b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887 . C\'f4 g\'e1i h\u7887 i c\u7853 u: "Tr\'ec Di\'ean anh \u273 eo g\'ec v\u7853 y? Th\u7853 t \u273 \u7897 c \u273 \'e1o th\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau, c\u361 ng t\u7863 ng em m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "Tro ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7869  kh\'f4ng g\'e2y ra b\'f3ng ma t\'e2m l\'fd c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i cho con nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i th\'eam b\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a, n\u7871 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\'f4 g\'e1i c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n vi\u7879 c c\u7853 u \u273 eo tro ng\u432 \u7901 i, ho\u7863 c c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7845 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7921 ng \u7903  trong b\'ecnh s\u7913  ch\'ednh l\'e0 tro ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7853 t, m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 c\u7853 u ch\u417 i th\'ec sao? V\u7915 a v\'e0o c\u7917 a, th\u7913  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean trong nh\'e0 ch\'ednh l\'e0 b\'e0i v\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ta: "B\'e0i v\u7883  n\'e0y anh kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 b\'e0y m\u7897 t ng\'e0y, anh mu\u7889 n b\'e0y c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i, sau n\'e0y ch\'fang ta c\'f3 nh\'e0 c\u361 ng v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i b\'e0y, m\u7897 t ng\'e0y th\u7855 p h\u432 \u417 ng ba l\u7847 n, c\u7909 c c\u432 ng \'e0 em n\u7845 u c\u417 m c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i n\u7845 u th\'eam m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n cho Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0o s\u7869  ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c vi\u7879 c n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ch\'ednh m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c r\'f5 r\'e0ng, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7921  m\'ecnh m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u7903  nh\'e0 \'f4m b\'e0i v\u7883  Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  s\u7889 ng qua m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i kh\u7843  thi h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7901  sau n\'e0y c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c kh\'f4ng c\'f2n b\u7853 n r\u7897 n n\u7919 a th\'ec tham gia m\u7897 t v\'e0i c\'e2u l\u7841 c b\u7897  th\u7875  thao, k\u7871 t giao b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u, nu\'f4i th\'fa c\u432 ng l\'e0m b\u7841 n v\u7899 i m\'ecnh. Suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng c\u361 ng r\u7845 t t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\uc0\u7921  m\'e0 kh\'e9o l\'e9o c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i mu\u7889 n gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng cho c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng nh\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ng\'e0y qua ng\'e0y l\'e0m b\u7841 n \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 em c\u7853 u nh\'e9t v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  hay bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \'c1i nh\'e2n c\uc0\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u7903  trong m\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \'97\'97 th\u7853 m ch\'ed ch\'ednh \'e1i nh\'e2n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\u361 ng cho l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n m\u417  \u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i b\u7845 t m\'e3n c\u7853 u b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c m\u417  \u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n mu\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  \'f4m l\u7841 i m\'ecnh, h\'f4n \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n mu\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  nh\'ecn v\'e0o m\u7855 t h\u7855 n, g\u7885 i t\'ean c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n mu\u7889 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t ng\'e0y cu\u7889 i th\'e1ng ba, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi ch\'ecm v\'e0o gi\u7845 c ng\u7911 . Kh\'ed tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 \u7845 m l\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng ban \u273 \'eam v\u7851 n h\u417 i l\u7841 nh nh\u432  c\u361 , trong l\'fac ng\u7911  m\u417  c\u7853 u th\u7845 y l\u7841 nh, v\'f4 th\u7913 c k\'e9o ch\u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" t\u7915  ph\'eda sau bao l\u7845 y c\u7853 u, m\u7897 t lu\u7891 ng kh\'ed \u273 en m\u7855 t th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ch\u7853 m r\'e3i x\'e2m nh\u7853 p v\'e0o trong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0m m\'ea t\'e2m tr\'ed, l\'e0m say l\'f2ng ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 G\uc0\u7885 i l\'e0, ma m\'ea qu\u7927  \'e1m.\cb1 \
