\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7921  nhi\'ean c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  r\'f5 b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\'ec sao quen nhau, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  r\'f5 th\'e2n ph\u7853 n lai l\u7883 ch c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 l\'fac c\u7853 u quay v\u7873  Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  th\u259 m ch\'fa m\u7907  r\u7891 i quen \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c tr\'ed nh\u7899  m\u417  h\u7891  n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u c\u7853 u, trong ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c c\'f3 m\u7897 t thanh \'e2m n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng sao c\u7843 , ch\u7881  c\u7847 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean nhau l\'e0 t\u7889 t r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao \'edt nh\uc0\u7845 t c\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\u7899  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\'f3 h\u7885  t\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n t\'ean Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Trong l\'f2ng im \u7855 ng l\u7863 p l\u7841 i c\'e1i t\'ean n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u7845 m \'e1p v\'e0 an to\'e0n, c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u417  h\u7891  tin c\u7853 y. Lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c t\'edn nhi\u7879 m n\'e0y l\'e0 th\u7913  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e0m gi\u7843  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec nguy\'ean nh\'e2n trong nh\'e0 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0m vi\u7879 c c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t h\u259 ng h\'e1i, \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p b\'ean c\u7841 nh \u273 \u7873 u nhao nhao tr\'eau gh\u7865 o n\'f3i tinh th\u7847 n c\u7853 u c\'f3 v\u7867  t\u7889 t l\'ean kh\'f4ng \'edt nha. C\'f2n c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i tr\'e1ch kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng cho c\u7853 u c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng th\'edch, h\'f3a ra l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m c\'f3 m\u7909 c ti\'eau ch\u7901  n\'ean chuy\u7879 n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i tu\u7847 n n\'e0y ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  n\u7889 i li\u7873 n v\u7899 i Qu\u7889 c t\u7871  lao \u273 \u7897 ng, k\'ec ngh\u7881  n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i ba ng\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7921  \u273 \u7883 nh t\u7921  l\'e1i xe mang Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i ra v\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i \'f4 ph\u7909  c\u7853 n ch\u417 i ba ng\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u x\'e1ch \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 \'e3 mua xong v\u7873  nh\'e0, c\'f2n ch\u432 a l\u7845 y ch\'eca kho\'e1 ra, c\u7917 a \u273 \'e3 m\u7903 , ph\'eda sau c\u7917 a ch\u7889 ng tr\u7897 m m\'e0u b\u7841 c l\u7897  ra khu\'f4n m\u7863 t t\u432 \u417 i c\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i cao ng\u7845 t c\u7911 a nam nh\'e2n \'f4n nhu tu\u7845 n m\u7929 , l\'e0 th\'e2n \u7843 nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean quen thu\u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'f4ng th\uc0\u7845 y h\u7855 n li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u cong kh\'f3e m\'f4i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7891  v\u7853 t b\u7883  m\u7845 t, vi\'ean m\'e3n. C\u7853 u ngh\u297  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 m\'ecnh r\u7845 t y\'eau ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n ti\uc0\u7871 p l\u7845 y \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, v\u7915 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a quen thu\u7897 c \u273 i v\'e0o trong b\u7871 p, m\u7897 t th\'e2n qu\u7847 n \'e1o b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u7903  nh\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  che h\u7871 t kh\'ed ch\u7845 t to\'e0n th\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, v\'ec v\u7853 y lu\'f4n c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7903  c\u7917 a tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7899  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n c\'f9ng \u273 \'e3 tr\'f4i qua bao l\'e2u, t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\u361 ng ch\u432 a l\'e2u l\u7855 m, l\u7841 i t\u7921 a h\u7891  \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\'e2u r\u7891 i. C\u7853 u nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\u432 ng nam nh\'e2n, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng. \u272 \'e1y l\'f2ng c\'f3 thanh \'e2m n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, th\u7871  n\'e0y l\'e0 \u273 \u7911  r\u7891 i, \u273 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng b\'ecnh y\'ean an \u7893 n m\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n theo \u273 u\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean b\'e0n c\uc0\u417 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean cao h\u7913 ng b\u7915 ng b\u7915 ng n\'f3i cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch \u273 i xa m\'e0 m\'ecnh s\u7855 p x\u7871 p, \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u361 a xu\u7889 ng tr\'f4ng mong nh\'ecn \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7907 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd nh\u432  c\u7853 u d\u7921  t\'ednh, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i ch\u7847 n ch\u7915  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\'ecn c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "Nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i \u273 i sao? Ch\'fang ta \u7903  trong nh\'e0 ch\u417 i kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'f9ng xu\uc0\u7889 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang \u273 u d\'e2y \u7903  n\u417 i cao l\u7853 p t\u7913 c r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng ch\u7895  th\u7845 p. Li\'ean t\u7909 c m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n c\u7853 u d\'f9ng th\u7901 i gian ngh\u7881  tr\u432 a xem x\'e9t c\'e1c \u273 \u7883 a \u273 i\u7875 m h\u7845 p d\u7851 n v\'e0 l\'ean k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch du l\u7883 ch, c\'f2n \u273 \u7883 nh d\u7915 ng ch\'e2n l\u7841 i, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 i du l\u7883 ch c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau h\u7871 t s\u7913 c ch\u7901  mong.\cb1 \
\cb3 "A," c\uc0\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng m\u7903  tr\'f2n m\u7855 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, "\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, anh kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i th\'ec ch\'fang ta s\u7869  ngh\u7881  l\u7877  \u7903  nh\'e0, tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  em s\u7869  mua th\u7853 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7891  \u259 n v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\'ean s\u7899 m nh\u7899  ra chuy\u7879 n Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng th\'edch \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, n\'f3i cho c\'f9ng c\u7853 u s\u7855 p x\u7871 p l\u7847 n \u273 i du l\u7883 ch n\'e0y c\u361 ng l\'e0 v\'ec \u273 \u7875  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng vui v\u7867 , \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ph\u7843 i nghe theo \'fd mu\u7889 n c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Song d\'f9 \uc0\u273 \'e3 ngh\u297  v\u7853 y, s\'e2u trong l\'f2ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t tia th\u7845 t l\u7841 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean k\'e9o tay c\u7853 u l\u7841 i, c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, t\'f4i hay n\'f3i \u273 \'f9a v\u7899 i em m\'e0, em th\u7853 t v\u7845 t v\u7843  m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i, ch\'fang ta \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ph\u7843 i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i ch\u417 i." B\u7897  d\u7841 ng h\u7855 n t\'f9y \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean th\u7853 t s\u7921  r\u7845 t \u273 \u7865 p, kh\'f3e m\u7855 t h\u417 i cong, trong \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u \u273 en t\u7921 a h\u7891  \u7849 n ch\u7913 a t\'ecnh \'fd v\'f4 h\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7889 c ng\u7889 c nh\'ecn h\u7855 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng \u273 \'ea\u777  \'fd \u273 \u234 \u769 n m\u7897 t kh\u7855 c do d\u7921  tuy\u7879 t kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng gi\u7843  b\u7897  kia c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u417  h\u7891  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7915  khi c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  b\'ean nhau, h\'e0nh vi c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 thay \u273 \u7893 i r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, trong cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, c\'f3 m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'f3 khi\u7871 n m\'ecnh m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u lo l\u7855 ng b\u7845 t an kh\'f4ng y\'ean, b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u259 n b\u7843 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\'e8m ngh\u297  t\u7899 i. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i qu\'ean m\u7845 t \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ng\u7851 m l\u7841 i c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i, c\'f3 ai sau khi y\'eau \u273 \u432 \u417 ng chung s\u7889 ng v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau v\u7851 n c\'f3 c\'e1ch s\u7889 ng nh\u432  khi c\'f2n \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n \u273 \'e2u?\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  ri\'eang chuy\u7879 n \u259 n u\u7889 ng n\'e0y, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7853 u s\u7889 ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, cho d\'f9 \u7903  nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 i l\'e0m c\u361 ng v\u7851 n th\u432 \u7901 ng g\u7885 i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n ngo\'e0i, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  m\u7895 i ng\'e0y c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i thay \u273 \u7893 i \u273 a d\u7841 ng \u273 \u7891  Trung \u273 \u7891  T\'e2y n\u7845 u cho c\u7853 u \u259 n, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y tan l\'e0m c\u7853 u c\'f2n ph\u7843 i nh\u7899  mua th\u7913 c \u259 n ng\'e0y mai mu\u7889 n \u259 n mang v\u7873 , \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean bi\u7871 n h\'f3a r\u7845 t l\u7899 n kh\'e1c nhau r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i m\u417  h\u7891  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c tr\u432 \u7899 c kia h\'ecnh nh\u432  m\'ecnh v\u7851 n th\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m th\'eam m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n c\u417 m, nh\u432 ng t\'ecm trong tr\'ed nh\u7899 , cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y ngh\uc0\u7881  \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n mang theo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ra c\u7917 a, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u m\u7897 t th\'e2n nh\'e0n nh\'e3, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f2n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\'ecm t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u ra m\u7897 t c\u7863 p k\'ednh r\'e2m, ng\u7891 i \u7903  v\u7883  tr\'ed k\u7871  b\'ean gh\u7871  l\'e1i, th\'e2n cao ch\'e2n d\'e0i kh\'ed th\u7871  m\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7847 n, t\u432  th\'e1i so ra c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng minh tinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi ng\uc0\u7891 i v\'e0o xe c\u7889  \'fd l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n x\u7845 u l\u7845 y k\'ednh r\'e2m h\u7855 n \u273 ang \u273 eo xu\u7889 ng, \'e1p l\u7841 i g\u7847 n h\'f4n nh\u7865  l\'ean m\'ed m\u7855 t h\u7855 n, nh\'ecn k\'ednh r\'e2m trong tay c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "\u272 \u7865 p \u273 \'f3, em c\u361 ng ch\u432 a th\u7845 y anh mang bao gi\u7901 , anh t\u7921  mua tr\'ean ph\u7889  sao?" C\u7853 u ch\'ednh l\'e0 thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i, trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7845 t \'edt khi c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ra \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u417  h\u7897 i th\u7845 y h\u7855 n mang k\'ednh r\'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u h\'f4n c\u432 \u7901 i h\'e0i l\'f2ng nheo l\u7841 i m\u7855 t, m\u417  h\u7891  l\'ean ti\u7871 ng: "Mua tr\u432 \u7899 c kia."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\'e1i xe theo \u7913 ng d\u7909 ng d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u7913 ng d\u7909 ng ch\u432 a c\u7853 p nh\u7853 t, c\'f3 m\u7897 t con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 ang s\u7917 a kh\'f4ng \u273 i qua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i quay l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u361  \u273 i m\u7897 t con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u361  \u273 i v\'f2ng v\'e8o khi\u7871 n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\'f4 l\u7921 c c\'f9ng m\u7879 t m\u7887 i \u273 au nh\u7913 c kh\u7855 p ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i d\'e2ng l\'ean, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng r\'ean l\'ean m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, em kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n l\'e1i xe n\u7919 a, anh l\'e1i thay em m\u7897 t l\'e1t \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'eam qua b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i t\u7889 t, s\'e1ng nay l\u7841 i d\u7853 y s\u7899 m, d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i l\'e1i xe, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i t\'ean \u273 \u7847 u s\u7887  g\'e2y t\u7897 i ham \u259 n kia l\u7841 i ung dung ng\u7891 i \u7903  gh\u7871  b\'ean c\u7841 nh nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t d\u432 \u7905 ng th\u7847 n?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u: "L\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? M\u7879 t r\u7891 i \u432 ? L\'e0 l\u7895 i c\u7911 a t\'f4i. B\u7843 o b\u7889 i em ch\u7883 u kh\'f3 ki\'ean tr\'ec th\'eam ch\'fat n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  m\u7897 t c\'e2u "B\u7843 o b\u7889 i" c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\'e0m cho \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a, r\u7845 t t\u7921  gi\'e1c ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c l\'e0m l\'e1i xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7893  sung: "Em qu\'ean r\u7891 i sao, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e1i xe, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7857 ng l\'e1i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 v\uc0\u7853 y \u432 ? Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i c\'f3 ch\'fat ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t, n\'e0y v\'e0 "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi" trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u h\'ecnh nh\u432  kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nhau l\u7855 m... Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  sao c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e1i xe? B\u7903 i v\'ec th\'e2n th\u7875  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n qu\'e1 k\'e9m \u432 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t chi\u7871 c xe ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c r\'edt l\'ean lao qua, c\u7853 u nhanh ch\'f3ng l\u7855 c l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, t\u7853 p trung tinh th\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  l\'e0 ai? V\'ec sao trong \u273 \u7847 u m\'ecnh l\u7841 i hi\u7879 n ra x\u432 ng h\'f4 nh\u432  th\u7871 ? Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e0u da h\u7855 n m\u7863 c d\'f9 c\'f3 ch\'fat t\'e1i nh\u7907 t, nh\u432 ng nguy\'ean nh\'e2n nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 v\'ec \u7903  m\'e3i trong nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i, nh\u432 ng t\u7889  ch\u7845 t c\u417  th\u7875  h\u7855 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng k\'e9m, c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y h\u7855 n sinh b\u7879 nh bao gi\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 ang s\u7917 a \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, xe t\u7843 i ch\u7903  v\u7853 t li\u7879 u lui t\u7899 i r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e1i xe kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ph\'e2n t\'e2m, c\u361 ng b\u7903 i v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng \u273 \'ea\u777  \'fd \u273 \u234 \u769 n m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7901  r\'f5 r\'e0ng\'97\'97 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  bi\u7871 t g\'ec v\u7873  nam nh\'e2n ng\'e0y qua ng\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u \u7845 p tay g\u7889 i m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n c\'f3 bi\u7871 t l\'e1i xe hay kh\'f4ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n c\'f3 bi\u7871 t b\u417 i hay kh\'f4ng, c\'f3 bi\u7871 t \u273 i xe \u273 \u7841 p hay kh\'f4ng... H\u7855 n r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c bi\u7871 t c\'e1i g\'ec kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'e1i g\'ec, th\'e2n ph\u7853 n h\u7855 n l\u7841 i l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, lai l\u7883 ch ra sao, trong nh\'e0 c\'f2n c\'f3 ai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\'fang ta \uc0\u273 \'e3 \u7903  b\'ean nhau g\u7847 n m\u7897 t n\u259 m r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7895  \u7903  \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m \u273 \u7863 t xong, l\'e0 thu\'ea c\u7911 a d\'e2n \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u417 ng. T\'f2a nh\'e0 hai t\u7847 ng, chia l\'e0m hai nh\'e0 tr\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i, kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n nhau, g\u7891 m c\'f3 ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p, ph\'f2ng \u259 n nh\u7887 , ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch v\'e0 m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , c\u7917 a s\u7893  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i c\u7843 nh h\u7891 , nghe n\'f3i l\'e0 ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng gi\'e1 \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t c\u7911 a trang web, \u7903  \u273 \'e2y v\'e0o th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m h\u7845 p d\u7851 n thu h\'fat kh\'e1ch du l\u7883 ch nh\u7845 t, thu\'ea m\u7897 t ng\'e0y c\u361 ng ch\u7881  h\u417 n hai tr\u259 m, v\'f4 c\'f9ng ph\'f9 h\u7907 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac b\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i v\u7915 a \u273 \'fang m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901  tr\u432 a, tr\u7901 i s\'e1ng r\'f5, ch\u7895  thu\'ea c\'f3 s\'e2n nh\u7887 , c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7895  xe. V\u7883  tr\'ed t\'f2a nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  thu\'ea c\'f3 ch\'fat \'e2m, nh\u432 ng t\u7847 m nh\'ecn r\u7845 t \u273 \u7865 p, \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i h\u7891  kh\'f4ng b\u7883  v\u7853 t g\'ec che ch\u7855 n. Nh\'e0 hai ba t\u7847 ng \u7903  quanh \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, nh\u432 ng tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn \'edt \u273 \u7875  \u7903  m\'e0 \u273 \u7841 i b\u7897  ph\u7853 n \u273 \u7873 u d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  cho du kh\'e1ch t\u7915  th\'e0nh th\u7883  g\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 t\u7921  l\'e1i xe \u273 i du l\u7883 ch \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y thu\'ea.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec l\'e0 chu\u7895 i ng\'e0y ngh\u7881 , d\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y xe t\u7915  n\u417 i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y du l\u7883 ch kh\'f4ng \'edt, c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'e0m \u259 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , l\u7847 u m\u7897 t ng\'f4i nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean thu\'ea l\u7841 i b\u7883  m\u7897 t \u7893  kh\'f3a l\u7899 n kh\'f3a l\u7841 i, b\'ean trong c\u7917 a s\u7893  t\u7889 i om, nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng r\'f5 l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7853 n ch\'eca kho\'e1 ph\'f2ng, thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i ch\u7911  nh\'e0 \u273 \u432 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i xem nh\'e0: "Ngh\u7881  l\u7877  l\'e0m \u259 n t\u7889 t th\u7871  n\'e0y, sao b\'e1c kh\'f4ng \u273 em l\u7847 u d\u432 \u7899 i cho thu\'ea \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7911  nh\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng h\u417 n b\u7889 n m\u432 \u417 i tu\u7893 i, nghe v\u7853 y h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\u7913 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t c\'e1i, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ch\'e0 x\'e1t tay n\'f3i: "Ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 ang tu s\u7917 a l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'f4ng v\uc0\u7899 i c\u7847 u thang l\u7847 u hai l\'e0 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c thang s\u7855 t b\u7855 c \u7903  b\'ean ngo\'e0i, thang \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u417 n m\'e0u xanh, c\'f3 v\'e0i ch\u7895  n\u432 \u7899 c s\u417 n \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  bong ra. Chi\u7871 c thang th\'f4ng v\u7899 i ban c\'f4ng l\u7847 u hai, l\'ean l\u7847 u m\u7903  c\u7917 a l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o nh\'e0. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe v\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, l\'fac xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u l\u7841 i v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua trong ph\'f2ng l\u7847 u m\u7897 t, c\u7917 a s\u7893  c\'f3 l\u7899 p b\u7909 i r\u7845 t d\'e0y, m\u7863 t tr\'ean c\'f2n s\u417 n tr\u7855 ng, cho n\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y r\'f5 l\u7855 m, nh\u432 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7901  m\u7901  th\u7845 y b\'ean trong ch\u7891 ng ch\u7845 t b\u7915 a b\'e3i l\u7897 n x\u7897 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy \uc0\u273 o\'e1n ch\u7855 c l\'e0 \u273 ang s\u7917 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t n\u7917 a, v\'ec v\u432 \u7899 ng c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c l\'e0m \u259 n \u273 ang t\u7889 t g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y, kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n g\'e2y \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n kh\'e1ch thu\'ea kh\'e1c n\'ean t\u7841 m th\u7901 i ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u432 a \u259 n tr\u432 a, sau khi c\u7845 t h\'e0nh l\'fd xong li\u7873 n l\'f4i k\'e9o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i \u259 n c\u417 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i t\u7921 a \u7903  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, xoa xoa tr\'e1n, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng t\u7921 a h\u7891  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 tho\u7843 i m\'e1i. H\u7855 n nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'f4n h\'f2a n\'f3i: "T\'f4i h\u417 i say xe, mu\u7889 n ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, em \u273 i \u259 n \u273 i? \u258 n xong mang g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 em v\u7873  cho t\'f4i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\uc0\u297  \u273 \u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng \u259 n g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, s\u7869  c\'e0ng th\'eam kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, li\u7873 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 i ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u417 i n\'e0y l\'e0 m\u7897 t thi\u803  tr\u7845 n nh\u7887  kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia v\u7851 n d\u7921 a v\'e0o n\'f4ng nghi\u7879 p l\'e0 ch\'ednh, m\u7845 y n\u259 m nay m\u7899 i ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n ng\'e0nh du l\u7883 ch, c\'e1c ti\u7879 m \u259 n \u273 \u7873 u r\u7853 p m\u7897 t khu\'f4n "L\'e0ng c\'e1 s\'f4ng" "Du l\u7883 ch n\u417 i th\'f4n d\'e3". Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7885 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t nh\'e0 nh\'ecn qua t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i s\u7841 ch s\u7869  \u273 i v\'e0o, g\u7885 i ba m\'f3n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n g\u7891 m c\u7843  c\u417 m \u273 \'f3ng g\'f3i l\u7841 i, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  mang v\u7873  c\'f9ng \u259 n v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng nhau \u259 n c\u417 m trong ph\'f2ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7905  r\u7891 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i ra b\'ean h\u7891  ch\u417 i, ng\u7855 m c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c h\'f3ng gi\'f3, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng s\u7869  tho\u7843 i m\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  c\'e1ch ch\u7895  \u7903  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng xa, \u273 i b\u7897  ch\u7881  ch\u7915 ng m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat. Kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i v\u7915 a \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'e1c g\'e1i ng\u259 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e1c g\'e1i h\uc0\u417 n n\u259 m m\u432 \u417 i tu\u7893 i, c\'e1ch \u259 n m\u7863 c kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c l\u7855 m so v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng tu\u7893 i \u7903  th\u7883  tr\u7845 n kh\'e1c, nh\'ecn qua b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec l\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u417 i n\'e0y g\u7847 n t\u7899 i ch\u7895  h\u7891 , nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ch\u7895  ch\'ednh, xung quanh t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i h\u7867 o l\'e1nh, b\u7889 n ph\'eda kh\'f4ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\'e0 ng\u259 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i, n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u t\u7917 , c\u7853 u th\u7871  n\'e0o l\u7841 i thu\'ea nh\'e0 l\'e3o H\u7891  kia?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n b\'e0, b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\u7915 a \u273 \u7843 o nhi\u7873 u m\'e1nh kho\'e9 b\u7883 p ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng l\u7855 m, \u7903  nh\u7919 ng \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\u7887  ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t c\u7849 n th\u7853 n, g\u7863 p ng\u432 \u7901 i k\u7923  qu\'e1i ti\u7871 n t\u7899 i h\u7887 i th\'ec tuy\u7879 t kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e1c g\'e1i kia v\uc0\u7851 n ch\u432 a t\u7915  b\u7887  \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh, b\'e1m theo n\'f3i: "Nh\'e0 ta c\u361 ng cho thu\'ea, c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng tr\u7889 ng \u7903  gi\u7919 a, t\'ednh r\u7867  cho c\u7853 u ch\u7881  t\'ednh 60% gi\'e1, c\u7853 u chuy\u7875 n qua \u273 \'f3 nh\'e9."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'ec ra l\'e0 m\uc0\u7901 i ch\'e0o thu\'ea nh\'e0. Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7841  c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c xu\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u7927  v\'e0o c\'f3 m\'ecnh v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi hai nam nh\'e2n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng b\u7855 t c\'f3c, li\u7873 n d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "B\'e1c g\'e1i, ch\'fang ch\'e1u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7863 t xong r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 \'e2u \u7841 , b\'e1c \u273 \u7915 ng b\u7853 n r\u7897 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y l\'e0m g\'ec, b\'e1c th\u7917  h\u7887 i nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c xem c\'f3 mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7863 t hay kh\'f4ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7883  b\'e1c g\'e1i kia \u273 \u7841 i th\u7845 y c\u7853 u d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i \u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i r\u7845 t ki\'ean nh\u7851 n, ch\u7847 n ch\u7915  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u huynh \u273 \u7879 , c\u7853 u nghe b\'e1c m\u7897 t c\'e2u, nh\'e0 l\'e3o H\u7891  kh\'f4ng s\u7841 ch s\u7869 , ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u7903  ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u th\'ec kh\'e1c, c\u7853 u th\u7875  ch\u7845 t c\u7921 c h\u432 ... N\'ean th\u7915 a d\u7883 p c\'f2n s\u7899 m chuy\u7875 n \u273 i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7875  ch\u7845 t c\u7921 c h\u432  l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec? Kh\'f4ng s\u7841 ch s\u7869  l\u7841 i l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng tin nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  m\'ea t\'edn c\u7893  h\u7911 , th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 trong tr\'ed nh\u7899  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u l\u7899 n cho \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y "Qu\u7927 " \u7903  trong phim ma.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t m\u7901  m\u7883 t, trong l\'f2ng ph\'e0n n\'e0n, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 m\u7845 y t\u7915  "Kh\'f4ng s\u7841 ch s\u7869 ", "C\u7921 c h\u432 " n\'e0y kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 ch\u7841 m \u273 \u7871 n s\u7907 i d\'e2y cung n\'e0o trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u, khi\u7871 n cho c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng l\'fd do run l\'ean, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7907  h\'e3i ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7921 c gi\'e1c khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n c\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\u7887 i k\u297  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\u432 ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u273 \'f3 m\u7897 t c\'e1nh tay \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ng\u259 n eo c\u7853 u l\u7841 i, v\'f2ng t\u7915  sau ra tr\u432 \u7899 c \'f4m l\u7845 y c\u7853 u, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gh\'e9 v\'e0o b\'ean tai c\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7841 t n\'f3i: "C\'f3 t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, em c\'f2n s\u7907  vi\u7879 c n\'e0y \u432 ."\cb1 \
