\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7919 a thanh thi\'ean b\u7841 ch nh\u7853 t \'f4m \'f4m \u7845 p \u7845 p th\u7871  n\'e0y l\'e0m Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y x\u7845 u h\u7893 , c\u7853 u th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i "\u272 \u7915 ng l\'e0m r\u7897 n", \u273 \u7849 y tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ra, kh\'f4ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7855 n \'f4m m\'ecnh l\'e0 \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng chi\u7871 m h\u7919 u c\u7905  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7907 i c\u7853 u t\u7915  ch\u7889 i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, b\'e1c g\'e1i kia l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 t\u7921  m\'ecnh b\u7887  \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297  ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  b\'e1c \u7845 y b\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  d\u7885 a s\u7907  r\u7891 i, ng\u7841 i \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ean kia, b\'e1c trai L\uc0\u432 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ph\'eda xa th\u7845 y v\u7907  m\'ecnh m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch tr\u7903  v\u7873 , d\u7909 i t\u7855 t \u273 i\u7871 u thu\u7889 c v\u7897 i v\'e0ng h\u7887 i: "Sao r\u7891 i? Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i n\'f3i mu\u7889 n l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n t\u7889 t t\'edch ph\'fac cho con ch\'e1u \u432 ? Sao l\u7841 i b\u7887  m\u7863 c \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean kia \u7903  nh\'e0 l\'e3o H\u7891 ? C\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean kia nh\'ecn qua s\u7869  *kh\'f4ng tr\u7845 n \'e1p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (Kh\'f4ng tr\uc0\u7845 n \'e1p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c: \'fd l\'e0 th\u7875  ch\u7845 t h\u432  nh\u432 \u7907 c y\u7871 u \u7899 t, kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ma qu\u7927 , ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7887 e m\u7841 nh th\'ec kh\'f4ng sao)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e1c g\'e1i L\uc0\u432 u ch\u7881  y\'ean l\u7863 ng l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e1c trai L\uc0\u432 u nh\'ecn s\u7855 c m\u7863 t v\u7907 , kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi c\'f9ng ch\u7891 ng \u273 i v\'e0o trong nh\'e0, b\'e1c g\'e1i L\u432 u m\u7899 i v\u7895  ng\u7921 c m\u7897 t c\'e1i, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai ch\u7891 ng n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean kia s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  th\u7913  l\u7907 i h\u7841 i h\u417 n qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e1c trai L\uc0\u432 u ch\u7845 n \u273 \u7897 ng, nh\'ecn tr\'e1i nh\'ecn ph\u7843 i, c\u361 ng nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "V\u7853 y b\'e0 kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  c\u7853 u ta m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e1c g\'e1i L\uc0\u432 u c\'fai th\u7845 p \u273 \u7847 u, m\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng d\'e1m."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\'e1t sau m\u7899 i h\u417 i d\'e3n ra t\u7915  trong n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i, b\'e0 m\u7899 i n\'f3i v\u7899 i ch\u7891 ng: "\'d4ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean \u273 \'f3 sao? Gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u273 i c\'f9ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u7853 u ta c\'f2n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i". Ch\'fang ta n\'ean nghi\'eam kh\u7855 c nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  t\u7909 i nh\u7887 , c\'e1ch...c\u7853 u ta xa m\u7897 t ch\'fat, tr\'e1nh cho va ch\u7841 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ai lo chuy\uc0\u7879 n c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3. B\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'e0nh th\'e0nh th\u7853 t th\u7853 t gi\u7919  khu\'f4n ph\'e9p m\'e0 s\u7889 ng, n\'e0o c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh qu\u7843 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n kia? L\'e3o H\u7891  b\u7883  ti\u7873 n t\'e0i m\'ea ho\u7863 c t\'e2m tr\'ed, bi\u7871 t r\'f5 c\u259 n nh\'e0 kia c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n cho thu\'ea, b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\u7871 u g\u7863 p ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7919 u duy\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7845 t h\u432  nh\u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng tr\u7845 n \'e1p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  th\'ec li\u7873 n nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  m\u7897 t c\'e2u, v\'ec con ch\'e1u m\'e0 t\'edch \u273 \u7913 c. Song h\'f4m nay ch\'e0ng trai kia nh\u432  v\u7853 y, cho d\'f9 \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn ra ch\'fat manh m\u7889 i, nh\u432 ng n\'e0o d\'e1m n\'f3i nhi\u7873 u m\u7897 t c\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i th\uc0\u7859 ng ra c\'e1i vi\u803  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" \u273 \'e2u, th\u7913  kia tr\u7843  th\'f9 ch\u7881  s\u7907  b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0n \uc0\u273 \'eam d\u7847 n d\u7847 n bu\'f4ng xu\u7889 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean mu\u7889 n k\'e9o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i \u259 n c\u417 m, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i n\'f3i: "L\'fac t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y t\'f4i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\'ean kia c\'f3 m\u7897 t ti\u7879 m b\'e1n c\'e1 v\u7899 i hoa qu\u7843  t\u432 \u417 i , ch\'fang ta mua v\u234 \u768  r\u7891 i t\'f4i l\'e0m cho em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'ecnh nh\uc0\u432  kh\'f4ng th\'edch \u259 n c\u417 m \u7903  ngo\'e0i. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u nh\'e0 h\'e0ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y tay ngh\u7873  qu\u7843  th\u7853 t c\'f3 h\u7841 n, ch\u7881  h\u417 n \u7903  nguy\'ean li\u7879 u n\u7845 u \u259 n m\u7899 i l\u7841  m\'e0 th\'f4i, mua v\u234 \u768  l\'e0m th\'ec c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u432 a bao gi\u7901  c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t y\'eau c\u7847 u c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau, l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u361 ng c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng. Trong l\'f2ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u b\u7853 t c\u432 \u7901 i ngh\u297 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng \u273 \'e3 h\u7841  c\u7893  m\'ecnh r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi tri\u7873 n mi\'ean h\u7891 i l\'e2u, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i m\u7879 t m\u7887 i v\'e0 bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 , v\u7915 a c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian tr\u7889 ng li\u7873 n ng\u7911  m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u, trong l\'fac n\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea c\u7853 u lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng n\u432 \u7899 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 v\u7915 a lao ra kh\u7887 i m\u7863 t n\u432 \u7899 c, m\'e0 th\u7913  kia \u273 ang\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1ch b\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng g\u7847 n...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tim c\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u273 \u7853 p nhanh m\u7897 t nh\u7883 p, s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7843  kinh, tho\'e1ng c\'e1i t\u7915  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng b\u7853 t d\u7853 y. Nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 , xuy\'ean qua khe h\u7903  c\u7917 a ch\u7899 p c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y r\'f5 s\'f3ng n\u432 \u7899 c c\'e1ch \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng xa l\u7845 p lo\'e1ng \u7903  tr\'ean m\u7863 t h\u7891 , trong b\'f3ng \u273 \'eam th\'e2m tr\u7847 m \'e1nh l\'ean tia s\'e1ng m\'e0u b\u7841 c.\cb1 \

