\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y tr\uc0\u7901 i trong, tr\u259 ng s\'e1ng sao th\u432 a, m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng. T\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u y\'ean t\u297 nh, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fat d\u7883  th\u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0o, r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p y\'ean b\'ecnh v\'f4 c\'f9ng c\u7911 a ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7903  ph\'e0o m\u7897 t h\u417 i, cho l\'e0 m\'ecnh m\u417  th\u7845 y \'e1c m\u7897 ng k\u7923  qu\'e1i. C\u7853 u li\u7871 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang an \u7893 n n\u7857 m b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh, h\'f4 h\u7845 p \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7863 n, c\'f3 ch\'fat lo l\u7855 ng qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u273 ang ng\u7911  say, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i, t\u7853 n l\u7921 c c\u7889  g\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7881 nh, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang n\u7917 a ng\u7891 i, c\u361 ng ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y \'f4m vai c\u7853 u, gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7851 n mang theo tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p c\'f9ng kh\'e0n kh\'e0n trong c\u417 n bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 : "L\'e0m sao v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, quay m\u7863 t sang \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t s\'e2u \u273 en c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, ch\u7881  l\'e0 g\u7863 p \'e1c m\u7897 ng th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ngay t\u432  th\u7871  ng\u7891 i \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u7903  b\'ean tai c\u7853 u h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i, tr\u7845 n an n\'f3i: "\u272 \u7915 ng s\u7907 , c\'f3 t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 v\'ec ban \u273 \'eam qu\'e1 l\u7841 nh qu\'e1 y\'ean t\u297 nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'ed t\u7913 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi phun v\'e0o l\u7895  tai m\'ecnh h\u417 i h\u417 i l\u7841 nh, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\'e1i \'f4m c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7845 m \'e1p m\'e0 h\u7919 u l\u7921 c nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng \u273 \'e8 xu\u7889 ng m\u417  h\u7891  b\u7845 t an trong l\'f2ng, k\'e9o ch\u259 n chu\u7849 n b\u7883  n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y, ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a vang l\'ean ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a "C\u7897 c c\u7897 c".\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'f2ng c\uc0\u7843  kinh, kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh n\'e0y c\'f3 ch\'fat quen thu\u7897 c, v\'f4 th\u7913 c quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c trong \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\u7903  to c\u7911 a c\u7853 u tr\'e0n \u273 \u7847 y s\u7907  h\'e3i v\'e0 b\u7845 t an, \u273 au l\'f2ng h\'f4n l\'ean m\'ed m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7909  h\'f4n nh\u432  l\'f4ng v\u361  r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng kia, v\'e0 c\u7843  thanh \'e2m c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, t\'f4i qua \u273 \'f3 xem m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7921  c\u7843 m ch\u7859 ng l\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c chi\u7871 m l\u7845 y tr\'e1i tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7853 u v\'f4 th\u7913 c l\'ean ti\u7871 ng: "\u272 \u7915 ng, Ngh\'eanh Chi, \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u mu\u7889 n n\'edu l\u7845 y v\u7841 t \'e1o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi, l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'fac ng\u7911  c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng m\u7863 c \'e1o, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7893 i th\'e0nh \'f4m l\u7845 y eo h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i ch\'f4n m\u7863 t \u7903  b\u7909 ng h\u7855 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "\u272 \u7915 ng \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a t\u7915 ng ti\u7871 ng t\u7915 ng ti\u7871 ng v\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361  kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng, nh\u432  \u7903  b\'ean tai, trong \u273 \'eam t\u7889 i y\'ean t\u297 nh l\u7841 i c\'e0ng th\'eam ch\'f3i tai, m\'e0 k\u7923  qu\'e1i h\u417 n n\u7919 a ch\'ednh l\'e0 ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7873 u tuy thong th\u7843  nh\u432 ng m\u7897 t l\u7847 n l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\'e0y t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  khi\u7871 n b\u7845 t c\u7913  ai ch\'fa \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i thu\u7853 n tay s\u7901  l\'ean t\'f3c c\u7853 u, tay tr\u432 \u7907 t xu\u7889 ng ph\u7911  \u7903  tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u, b\u7853 t c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "Th\u7871  n\'e0y l\'e0 sao \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng ph\'e1t gi\'e1c \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh qu\'e1 gi\u7889 ng con n\'edt, \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t h\u417 i h\u417 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7895  v\u7895  vai c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "T\'f4i \u273 i xem th\u7917 , r\u7845 t nhanh s\u7869  quay l\u7841 i, em c\u7913  ng\u7911  \u273 i." D\u7913 t l\u7901 i nhanh ch\'f3ng tr\u7903  m\'ecnh xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i gi\'e0y, kh\'f4ng cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u417  h\u7897 i gi\u7919  l\u7841 i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\uc0\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda huy\u7873 n quan, n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i t\u7921 a nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng tr\u7843 i qua gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 n\u7893 i l\'ean trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u \'97\'97 con m\u7855 t tr\u7855 ng xanh, ng\u7885 n \u273 \'e8n tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch, ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7873 u v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng d\u7913 t, b\'e0i v\u7883  m\'e0u \u273 en...\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i c\uc0\u7917 a... Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec \uc0\u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng m\u7845 y th\u7913  n\'e0y, h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 nghe l\u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ch\u7881  c\'e1ch, c\u7889  \'fd th\u7881 nh b\'e0i v\u7883  ai \u273 \'f3 v\'e0o trong nh\'e0, nh\u432 ng \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 b\'e0i v\u7883  c\u7911 a ai, ph\'eda tr\'ean ghi g\'ec... \u272 \'f3 l\'e0, t\'ean ai...\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y "K\'e9t..." m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\u7917 a m\u7903 , nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng n\'e0o kh\'e1c truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1p l\u7841 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng suy ngh\u297  k\u7923  qu\'e1i m\'e0 r\u7889 i lo\u7841 n trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \'e1p \u273 \u7871 n v\'ec lo l\u7855 ng cho ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i nh\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, g\u7841 ch tr\'e1ng men l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o k\'edch th\'edch c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i t\u7915  trong tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n, l\u7841 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7863 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'e9o c\u7853 u l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'e9t v\'e0o trong ch\u259 n, v\u7915 a nh\'e9t v\u7915 a qu\u7903  tr\'e1ch: "T\'f4i n\'f3i ch\u7881  \u273 i nh\'ecn m\u7897 t c\'e1i, sao em l\u7841 i ra r\u7891 i? C\'f2n kh\'f4ng m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o. Ch\u7895  n\'e0y bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i l\u7841 nh, b\u7883  l\u7841 nh sinh b\u7879 nh th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngoan ngo\'e3n b\uc0\u7883  h\u7855 n nh\'e9t tr\u7903  v\u7873 , nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau, nh\u7919 ng \'fd ni\u7879 m l\u7897 n x\u7897 n m\'e0 qu\u7927  d\u7883  trong \u273 \u7847 u nh\'e1y m\u7855 t v\u7915 a r\u7891 i li\u7873 n tan th\'e0nh m\'e2y kh\'f3i. C\u7853 u c\u7921 a qu\u7853 y n\u7857 m b\'ean c\u7841 nh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec v\u7853 y?" Ngay l\'fac Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7903  c\u7917 a ra, ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a b\'ean ngo\'e0i li\u7873 n bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, t\'f4i m\u7903  c\u7917 a b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 ai \u273 \'f3 u\u7889 ng say, t\'ecm nh\u7847 m c\u7917 a, \u273 \'fang l\'fac t\'f4i m\u7903  th\'ec ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra n\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'f3i: "Nh\u432 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng m\u7897 t gi\'e2y tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac anh m\u7903  c\u7917 a v\u7851 n c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'f5 c\u7917 a m\'e0, ch\'fang ta \u7903  l\u7847 u hai, d\'f9 c\'f3 \u273 i ngay l\'fac \u273 \'f3 th\'ec anh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i ta." Hu\u7889 ng chi s\u7869  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i u\u7889 ng say g\'f5 c\u7917 a \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7873 u theo nh\u7883 p l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y sao? Th\u7853 m ch\'ed... s\u7869  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'f5 c\u7917 a nh\u432  v\u7853 y sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i b\'e1c g\'e1i n\'f3i l\'fac chi\u7873 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean chui v\'e0o trong \u273 \u7847 u \'97\'97 "Nh\'e0 l\'e3o H\u7891  kh\'f4ng s\u7841 ch s\u7869 ..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\'f9ng m\'ecnh m\u7897 t c\'e1i, l\u7841 i r\u7909 t v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7897 ng t\'e1c y\u7871 u th\u7871  \u7927  l\u7841 i t\'ecm ki\u7871 m che ch\u7903  n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean l\u7845 y l\'f2ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\'e0o \'f4m th\u7853 t ch\u7863 t, h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i l\'ean \u273 \u7881 nh \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u, b\'e0n tay v\u7895  v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7907 t tr\'ean t\u7845 m l\u432 ng tr\u417 n nh\u7861 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, m\u417  h\u7891  n\'f3i: "... B\'ean ngo\'e0i qu\'e1 t\u7889 i, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 t\'f4i kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y r\'f5. Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'e2u, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i x\u7845 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1nh l\u7841 i t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\uc0\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, tay tr\'e1i n\'e2ng m\u7863 t c\u7853 u l\'ean nh\'ecn v\'e0o m\u7855 t c\u7853 u: "B\u7843 o b\u7889 i, em s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  tin l\u7901 i b\'e0 c\u7909  n\'f3i l\'fac chi\u7873 u cho l\'e0 c\'f3 qu\u7927  ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 c\uc0\u7909  c\'e1i g\'ec h\u7843 , b\'e1c g\'e1i \u273 \'f3 r\'f5 r\'e0ng ch\u432 a c\'f3 gi\'e0. X\u7845 u h\u7893  v\'ec b\u7883  ch\u7885 c th\u7911 ng kh\'fac m\u7855 c c\'f9ng v\u7899 i th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  tr\'eau ch\u7885 c c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t, kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u m\u7903  m\u7855 t n\'f3i: "\u272 \'e2u c\'f3, em m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng tin."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh tr\uc0\u259 ng xuy\'ean qua khe h\u7903  c\u7917 a ch\u7899 p chi\u7871 u v\'e0o, chi\u7871 u l\'ean g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t h\u7891 ng h\u7891 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897 ng l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'f4n l\'ean, trong mi\u7879 ng l\u7849 m b\u7849 m n\'f3i: "Em th\u7845 y t\'f4i gi\u7889 ng qu\u7927  hay kh\'f4ng... gi\u7889 ng \'e1c qu\u7927  hay kh\'f4ng, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 em em ng\u7853 m v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng, h\u7911 y \u273 i \u259 n v\'e0o trong b\u7909 ng..."\cb1 \
