\cb3 K\uc0\u7871  ho\u7841 ch c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  n\'e0y \u7903  hai ng\'e0y ch\u417 i ba ng\'e0y, ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng s\u7869  ch\u7841 y v\u7873  T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883 . K\u7871 t qu\u7843  bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean b\u7903 i v\'ec chuy\u7879 n g\'f5 c\u7917 a m\'e0 n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, l\u7841 i c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u259 n qua l\u259 n l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n h\u7915 ng \u273 \'f4ng, th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n b\u7889 n n\u259 m gi\u7901  s\'e1ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u7911 , l\'fac t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y th\'ec \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 gi\u7919 a tr\u432 a m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901 , v\u7853 y m\'e0 m\u7897 t n\u7917 a ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  \u273 \'e3 qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i, h\'e0i l\'f2ng th\u7887 a m\'e3n n\u7857 m b\'ean c\u7841 nh nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, th\u7845 y c\u7853 u t\u7881 nh li\u7873 n \'e1p s\'e1t t\u7899 i h\'f4n nh\u7865  l\'ean m\'ed m\u7855 t c\u7853 u: "Ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7911  ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u7903  tay nh\u7845 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c g\u7889 i \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean \u273 \u7853 p t\u7899 i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi anh c\'f3 th\u7853 t l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng? N\'e0o c\'f3 ai h\u417 n n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam c\'f3 tinh th\u7847 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t tay c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 i hung kh\'ed \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i m\u7903  r\u7897 ng v\'f2ng tay, tr\'e1i l\u7841 i t\u7887  ra y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng nhung nh\u7899  Tr\'ec Di\'ean. H\u7855 n vu\u7889 t ve c\u7893  Tr\'ec Di\'ean, r\u7845 t vui v\u7867  m\'e0 n\'f3i: "\u272 \'e2u c\'f3, em nguy\u7879 n \'fd b\u7891 i t\'f4i th\'ec ban ng\'e0y t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\'f3 tinh th\u7847 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean mu\uc0\u7889 n t\u7889 ng h\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n v\u259 n ph\'f2ng t\'e2n khu Hoa Dung \u273 \u7875  c\u7843 i t\u7841 o gi\'e1o d\u7909 c l\u7841 i, ti\u7871 p thu ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a x\'e3 h\u7897 i v\u259 n minh khoa h\u7885 c m\u7899 i. Nh\u432 ng b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n l\u7901 i n\'f3i hay h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng d\'f9 c\u7921  n\u7921  th\u7871  n\'e0o, trong l\'f2ng v\u7851 n r\u7845 t ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\u7853 u tr\u7901 i sinh n\'ean th\'edch ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y nh\u432  th\u7871 , c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y h\u7855 n, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u7903  b\'ean h\u7855 n, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7855 n \'f4m, li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y vui m\u7915 ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng th\u7875  k\'ecm n\'e9n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, t\u432 \u7903 ng nh\u432  mu\u7889 n kh\'f3c l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\u7913  h\u7891  nh\'e1o nh\u432  v\u7853 y qu\u7843  th\u7921 c m\'e3i kh\'f4ng d\u7913 t, b\u7919 a tr\u432 a c\u361 ng \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u432 a th\u7859 ng t\u7899 i c\u7917 a, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y du l\u7883 ch v\u7889 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \u7875  th\u7843  l\u7887 ng, tho\u7843 i m\'e1i th\u7871  n\'e0o vui v\u7867  th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u7913  t\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 i ra ngo\'e0i l\u7845 y \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7887 i c\'f4 g\'e1i \u273 \u432 a c\u417 m ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  h\u7891  n\u432 \u7899 c ra th\'ec c\'f2n ch\u7895  n\'e0o c\u7843 nh \u273 \u7865 p ch\u417 i vui n\u7919 a, c\'f4 g\'e1i n\'f3i n\'f3i ph\'eda \u273 \'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u7885 n n\'fai, ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng khai ph\'e1, nh\u432 ng kh\'e1ch du l\u7883 ch t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7873 u n\'f3i c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , u t\u297 nh m\'e0 th\'fa v\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  v\'ec gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng k\u7923  qu\'e1i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng \u273 u\'f4i h\'f4m qua, Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng sinh ra \u273 \u7889 i ngh\u7883 ch v\u7899 i h\u7891  n\u432 \u7899 c kia, nh\u432 ng m\'e0... hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n leo n\'fai.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n m\'e0 th\'e0nh th\u7853 t n\'f3i: "Ch\'fang ta ch\u417 i \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quy\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh v\u7851 n l\'e0 \u273 i ng\u7855 m h\u7891 . \u7902  n\u417 i n\'e0y c\u7843 nh h\u7891  n\u7893 i danh nh\u7845 t, ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7881  l\u432 \u7907 n quanh ch\u7895  h\u7867 o l\'e1nh, ch\u432 a \u273 i ch\u417 i ch\u7895  phong c\u7843 nh \u273 \'f4ng kh\'e1ch du l\u7883 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7895  b\'ean b\'ean kia t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t, c\'f3 c\u7843  du thuy\u7873 n, m\'f4 t\'f4 tr\'ean n\u432 \u7899 c, ca n\'f4 v\'e0 c\'e1c lo\u7841 i vui ch\u417 i kh\'e1c, du thuy\u7873 n mua v\'e9 ng\u7891 i theo gh\u7871  c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7913 a m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  thu\'ea thuy\u7873 n t\u7921  \u273 \u7841 p ch\u7903  t\u7889 i \u273 a b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i: "Ch\'fang ta thu\'ea thuy\u7873 n t\u7921  \u273 \u7841 p \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn nh\'ecn, qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean \u273 i thuy\u7873 n kh\'e1 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c y\'eau th\'edch, m\u7897 t nh\'e0 ba ng\u432 \u7901 i ho\u7863 c l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau nhau c\'f3 \u273 \'f4i c\'f3 c\u7863 p \u273 \u7873 u th\'edch thu\'ea thuy\u7873 n t\u7921  \u273 \u7841 p hay ng\u7891 i thuy\u7873 n h\u417 n l\'e0 \u273 i ch\u417 i trong \u273 o\'e0n ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 i ra ch\u7895  n\u7897 p ti\u7873 n thu\'ea thuy\u7873 n l\'e0m th\u7911  t\u7909 c, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng trung ni\'ean ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch th\u7845 y c\u7853 u m\u7897 t m\'ecnh m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, nhi\u7873 u l\u7901 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "Ch\'e0ng trai sao c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7891 i thuy\u7873 n? C\u7843 nh n\'ean ng\u7855 m \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i t\u7899 i, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 \u7841 p, gi\'e1 c\u7843  c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i ch\u259 ng h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u." Thuy\u7873 n thu\'ea l\'fac n\'e0y r\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 t kh\'e1ch, m\u7897 t h\u7891 i n\u7919 a ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i s\u7869  c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n, kh\'f4ng lo kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i thu\'ea, ch\u7881  m\u7899 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n m\'e0 trong thuy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 ng\u7891 i k\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i. H\u7855 n v\u7851 n mu\u7889 n nh\'e2n c\u417  h\u7897 i ch\'e0o h\'e0ng nh\u7919 ng h\'ecnh th\u7913 c kh\'e1c, ch\'e0o h\'e0ng c\'e1c c\u7863 p \u273 \'f4i ho\u7863 c l\'e0 c\'e1c gia \u273 \'ecnh th\'ec kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7855 m, thanh ni\'ean kia ch\u7881  \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  c\'e2n nh\u7855 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n v\u7915 a n\'f3i xong c\'e2u \u273 \'f3, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y sau g\'e1y l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o, \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i run l\'ean, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i r\u7909 t c\u7893  m\u7897 t c\'e1i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n t\'e2m t\'ecnh ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ch\'e0o h\'e0ng n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e3 nh\u7863 n t\u7915  ch\u7889 i: "Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n." C\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u273 i ch\u417 i, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\'f3 kh\'f4ng gian t\u432  m\u7853 t kh\'f4ng b\u7883  qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u s\u7869  tho\u7843 i m\'e1i vui v\u7867  h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  n\'e0y g\u7885 i l\'e0 h\u7891  N\u7919  Nhi, tuy n\'f3i l\'e0 h\'ecnh tr\u259 ng l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7873 m, nh\u432 ng k\u7923  th\u7853 t ph\u7847 n u\u7889 n cong \u7903  gi\u7919 a c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng ph\u7859 ng, gi\u7889 ng h\'ecnh ch\u7919  "K" h\u417 n. M\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec nguy\'ean nh\'e2n \u273 \u7883 a th\u7871  d\'e1ng n\'fai, hai b\'ean ch\u7895  u\u7889 n cong c\u7911 a h\u7891  n\u432 \u7899 c v\u7915 a \u273 \'fang b\u7883  chia th\'e0nh hai m\u7863 t \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng, m\u7897 t b\'ean \'e1nh s\'e1ng m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7911 , m\u7863 t h\u7891  \'e1nh kim; m\u7863 t b\'ean kia th\'ec l\u7841 i u t\u297 nh r\'e2m m\'e1t. \u272 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i qu\'e1n tr\u7885  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7863 t \'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u417 i cho thu\'ea thuy\u7873 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7889  tr\'ed \u7903  b\'ean m\u7863 t d\u432 \u417 ng, t\u432 \u417 ng \u7913 ng theo \u273 \'f3 kh\'e1ch v\u7899 i thuy\u7873 n b\'ean n\'e0y c\u361 ng nhi\u7873 u, v\'f4 c\'f9ng n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t, qua ch\u7895  u\u7889 n cong kia thuy\u7873 n li\u7873 n \'edt h\u7859 n \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  ch\u7881  ph\u7847 n h\u7891  u\u7889 n cong n\u417 i xa: "A Di\'ean, \u7903  \u273 \'e2y nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i qu\'e1, ch\'fang ta qua b\'ean kia \u273 i. Em \u273 \u7841 p tr\u432 \u7899 c, ch\u7901  t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3 \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i l\u7841 i thay em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\uc0\u7883  ngh\u7883  g\'ec, nghe l\u7901 i \u273 \u7841 p thuy\u7873 n v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'ean kia, sau khi \u273 \u7871 n m\u7863 t \'e2m c\u7911 a h\u7891 , thuy\u7873 n t\u7921  \u273 \u7841 p c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 l\u7867  t\u7867  hai c\'e1i, ho\'e0n to\'e0n b\u7845 t \u273 \u7891 ng v\u7899 i c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t c\'e1ch ba b\u7889 n m\'e9t xung quanh l\u7841 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3, l\'fac n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\u7843  nhi\'ean \u273 \u7843 m nhi\u7879 m nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  l\'e1i thuy\u7873 n, \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i ng\u7855 m c\u7843 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ean c\uc0\u7841 nh c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c thuy\u7873 n h\u417 i g\u7847 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i ng\u432 \u7907 c qua, b\'e9 trai b\'ean trong \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ch\u7881  v\'e0o thuy\u7873 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\'f4: "M\u7865  \u417 i, m\u7865  \u417 i, sao thuy\u7873 n c\u7911 a ch\'fa kia kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 \u7841 p kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n n\u7855 m tay l\'e1i v\u7851 n \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i m\u7865  tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i quan s\'e1t chi\u7871 c thuy\u7873 n ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 thuy\u7873 n d\'f9ng ch\'e2n \u273 \u7841 p gi\u7889 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 nh\uc0\u7865  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i con trai: "Nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 con nh\'ecn l\u7847 m r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f4 v\'e0 ch\u7891 ng mang theo con nh\u7887  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y ch\u417 i, sau \u273 \'f3 hai \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  nh\u7899  m\'e3i kh\'f4ng qu\'ean tr\'f2 \u273 \u7841 p thuy\u7873 n n\'e0y, c\'f4 v\u7899 i ch\u7891 ng c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 h\u7865 n v\u7899 i hai \u273 \u7913 a con ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  l\u7847 n n\'e0y s\u7869  l\u7841 i d\u7851 n c\'e1c con \u273 \u7871 n, ai ng\u7901  s\u7855 p \u273 \u7871 n ng\'e0y \u273 i th\'ec ch\u7891 ng l\u7841 i ph\u7843 i \u273 i c\'f4ng t\'e1c. Hai ti\u7875 u gia h\u7887 a t\u7915  m\'f9a thu n\u259 m ngo\'e1i \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7901  mong h\u417 n n\u7917 a n\u259 m, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'e1c, c\'f4 \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i t\u7921  m\'ecnh mang con trai b\u7843 y tu\u7893 i c\'f9ng con g\'e1i ba tu\u7893 i r\u432 \u7905 i \u273 i ch\u417 i. Nh\u432 ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u7913 ng ph\'f3 hai \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  n\'e0y c\u361 ng khi\u7871 n c\'f4 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 u\u7889 i s\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y con g\'e1i v\uc0\u7851 n lu\'f4n y\'ean l\u7863 ng ng\u7891 i \u259 n ng\u7855 m c\u7843 nh b\'ean ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "Anh hai n\'f3i x\u7841 o! B\'ean c\u7841 nh ch\'fa \u7845 y c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fa kh\'e1c \u273 ang l\'e1i thuy\u7873 n. Con c\'f2n tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t c\'f4 mu\u7889 n b\'f2 l\'ean thuy\u7873 n c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885 , b\u7883  ch\'fa kia \u273 \u7841 p xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Anh trai b\'e9 g\'e1i b\uc0\u7845 t m\'e3n b\u7883  em g\'e1i t\u7889  c\'e1o oan, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean cau m\'e0y n\'f3i: "Anh kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i! Trong thuy\u7873 n \u273 \'f3 ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fa th\'f4i! Nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 m\u7865  c\u361 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y!" B\'e9 n\'f3i xong li\u7873 n chuy\u7875 n h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919 , mu\u7889 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7865  m\'ecnh \u7911 ng h\u7897 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng ch\u7907 t l\u7841 nh, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i con trai n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3. Con g\'e1i m\u7899 i ba tu\u7893 i r\u432 \u7905 i, c\'f3 ai d\u7841 y n\'f3 n\'f3i lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y sao? N\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai d\u7841 y, l\'e0m sao n\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  m\'ecnh b\u7883 a ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 v\'e0 con trai r\'f5 r\'e0ng \uc0\u273 \u7873 u tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y trong chi\u7871 c thuy\u7873 n kia ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i...\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c qu\'e1t l\u7899 n m\u7855 ng con trai ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7897 n x\u7897 n, l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 a tay \'f4m con g\'e1i \u273 \u7863 t \u7903  gi\u7919 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 con trai, b\u7843 n th\'e2n d\'f9ng h\u7871 t s\u7913 c l\u7921 c \u273 \u7841 p b\'e0n \u273 \u7841 p l\'e1i thuy\u7873 n tr\u7903  v\u7873 , th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi c\'e1ch ch\u7895  thu\'ea thuy\u7873 n ven b\u7901  c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, th\u7845 y xung quanh nhi\u7873 u thuy\u7873 n h\u417 n m\u7899 i bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng tr\'e1i tim \u273 ang treo xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng c\'f4 kh\'f4ng kh\uc0\u7887 i sinh ra v\'e0i ph\u7847 n o\'e1n gi\u7853 n ch\u7891 ng, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\'e1ch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u361 ng kh\'f3 m\'e0 ch\u7881  tr\'edch \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng b\u7873  b\u7897 n nhi\u7873 u vi\u7879 c. Nh\'ecn s\u7855 c tr\u7901 i th\u7847 m ngh\u297  h\'f4m nay \u273 \'e3 mu\u7897 n, \u7903  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam, s\'e1ng mai s\u7869  mang hai con v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7841 p b\'e0n \u273 \u7841 p, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  d\u7845 u v\u7871 t du\u7895 i ch\'e2n tr\'e1i ra, h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda b\u7889 n ng\'f3n tay tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch ph\'f9 th\u361 ng \u273 ang b\'e1m l\'ean m\'e9p thuy\u7873 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh t\'e0n nh\u7851 n \u273 \u7841 p xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
