\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'eam nay tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7847 y m\'e2y, qu\u7847 ng tr\u259 ng s\'e1ng d\u7847 n d\u7847 n b\u7883  t\u7847 ng m\'e2y bao ph\u7911 , tr\'ean m\u7863 t h\u7891  c\u361 ng n\u7893 i l\'ean t\u7847 ng m\u7897 t s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9, b\'f3ng \u273 \'eam t\u297 nh l\u7863 ng nh\u432  c\u361 , l\u7841 i d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  ti\u7873 m \u7849 n th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m x\'fac kinh ho\u7843 ng s\u7907  h\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  \'e1p ch\u7871 , c\u7853 u b\u7845 t ch\u7845 p s\u7869  qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau, \'fap s\u7845 p l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m l\u7845 y h\u7855 n, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng k\'eau l\'ean: "Ngh\'eanh Chi..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7853 p t\u7913 c m\u7903  m\u7855 t, b\'ecnh t\u297 nh \'f4m l\u7841 i c\u7853 u, an \u7911 i: "\u272 \u7915 ng s\u7907 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c s\u7869  c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  h\u417 n ph\'e1t sinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7897 c c\u7897 c", ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a vang l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7917 a b\u7885 n h\u7885 , c\'f2n c\'f3 c\u7917 a l\u7847 u d\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e0ng th\'eam qu\uc0\u7927  d\u7883  l\'e0, theo m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng "K\'e9t..", c\u259 n ph\'f2ng d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u kia kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai \u7903 , ch\u7911  nh\'e0 n\'f3i l\'e0 \u273 ang l\u7855 p \u273 \u7863 t thi\u7871 t b\u7883 , c\'e1nh c\u7917 a c\u361  k\u7929  kia th\u7871  m\'e0 l\u7841 i m\u7903  ra theo ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a. Ti\u7871 ng m\u7903  c\u7917 a c\u7921 c k\u7923  r\'f5 r\'e0ng truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean tai c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7851 n \u273 ang ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c, d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u r\u7891 i l\u7841 i vang l\'ean ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng s\u7897 t so\u7841 t, t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 di chuy\u7875 n nh\u432  \u273 ang b\'f2 r\u7841 p tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tri\uc0\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901 , b\u7883  hai lo\u7841 i \'e2m thanh \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i t\u7891 n t\u7841 i n\'e0y qu\u7845 y \u273 \u7871 n v\'f4 l\u7921 c suy ngh\u297 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  g\u7855 ng g\u432 \u7907 ng duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  \'f4m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng v\u7895  l\u432 ng c\u7853 u an \u7911 i, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n l\'ean m\'ed m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng run run c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng qu\'ean \u273 \u432 a tay \u273 em to\'e0n b\u7897  s\u7889 ng l\u432 ng b\u7883  l\u7897  ra ngo\'e0i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u nh\'e9t v\u7873  trong ch\u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng b\'f2 r\u7841 p d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u kia c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng, c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, sau \u273 \'f3 h\'ecnh nh\u432  thay \u273 \u7893 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u432 \u7899 ng... Th\u7913  kia b\'f2 l\'ean t\u432 \u7901 ng, ch\'ednh l\'e0 b\u7913 c t\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  d\u7921 a v\'e0o! C\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng m\'f3ng tay c\'e0o tr\u7847 n nh\'e0, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7885 i ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7873 u ng\u432 ng\'97\'97 nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\u7871 t, th\u7913  kia d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\'ean tr\u7847 n nh\'e0 l\u7847 u d\u432 \u7899 i, \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i g\u7847 m gi\u432 \u7901 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u ngay c\u7843  \u273 \u7841 p c\u7917 a m\'e0 ch\u7841 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m, b\u7903 i v\'ec ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a c\'f3 nh\u7883 p v\u7851 n \u273 ang ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m g\'e2y ra ti\uc0\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng, ngay c\u7843  th\u7903  c\u361 ng c\u7849 n th\u7853 n t\u7915 ng ch\'fat, c\u7853 u s\u7907  "Th\u7913  kia" \u7903  ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i nghe th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7921 c k\u7923  c\u7849 n th\u7853 n ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean tai Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... Ngh\'eanh Chi, anh nghe th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong b\'f3ng t\uc0\u7889 i, m\u7855 t s\u7855 c c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7903  n\'ean c\u7921 c k\u7923  th\'e2m tr\u7847 m, h\u7855 n cong cong kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng, l\u7847 m r\u7847 m m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "To gan l\u7899 n m\u7853 t." \u272 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i tay v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng qu\'ean ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c tr\u7845 n an ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u7887 i: "Anh n\'f3i g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i: "T\'f4i n\'f3i chu\u7897 t b\'e2y gi\u7901  gan th\u7853 t l\u7899 n, may m\'e0 nh\'e0 ch\'fang ta kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chu\u7897 t. C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 ai \u273 \'e1ng gh\'e9t nh\u432  v\u7853 y ng\'e0y n\'e0o c\u361 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a, \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i \u273 i xem l\u7847 n n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7897  ch\u7859 ng h\u7873  \u273 \u7875  \'fd c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\u361 ng \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng kinh ho\u7843 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y n\u7919 a: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i chu\u7897 t, anh nghe ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng kia \u273 i, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i chu\u7897 t c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t ra."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 em Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i lo l\u7855 ng n\'e2ng n\u7917 a ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean nh\'e9t v\u7873  trong ch\u259 n, b\u7843 n th\'e2n ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y chu\u7849 n b\u7883  xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng n\'f3i: "\u7914 , lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u417 ng d\u7921 a n\'fai k\u7873  s\'f4ng n\'e0y c\'e1c lo\'e0i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t hoang d\'e3 nhi\u234 \u768 u, c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 ch\u7891 n ho\u7863 c t\'ea t\'ea g\'ec \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7891 n? T\'ea t\'ea?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  nh\u7887  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7889 ng \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889 , \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7845 y lo\'e0i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7881  nghe danh m\'e0 ch\u432 a th\u7845 y m\u7863 t, c\'f9ng l\u7855 m l\'e0 th\u7845 y \u7903  tr\'ean tivi, ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7921 c s\u7921  ti\u7871 p x\'fac, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng s\'e2u s\u7855 c g\'ec l\u432 u l\u7841 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ch\'fang r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c h\'ecnh d\u7841 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, t\u7853 p t\'ednh ra sao. Nghe xong l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i, c\u361 ng th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'e0 m\'ecnh suy ngh\u297  nhi\u7873 u, t\u7921  m\'ecnh d\u7885 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng li\'ean t\u7909 c hai ng\'e0y ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u vang l\'ean sau khi c\u7853 u m\u417  th\u7845 y \'e1c m\u7897 ng v\u7851 n r\u7845 t d\u7885 a ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \'f4m l\u7845 y eo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7915  ph\'eda sau: "Ngh\'eanh Chi anh \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 i qua \u273 \'f3, anh \u7903  l\u7841 i v\u7899 i em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng... Ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c, ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c ng\'e0y mai tr\u7901 i s\'e1ng t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng sao n\u7919 a." C\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0 t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c "Ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c l\'e0 t\u7889 t r\u7891 i" n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i s\u7901  s\u7901  m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, nh\u7899  t\u7899 i b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\u7853 u l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c b\u7883  d\u7885 a \u273 \u7871 n hai m\u7855 t \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng kh\'f3c l\'ean, khuy\'ean nh\u7911  n\'f3i: "T\'f4i \u273 i nh\'ecn th\u7917  gi\u7889 ng h\'f4m qua th\'f4i, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh v\u7851 n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua, h\'f4m nay l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n nh\u7847 m c\u7917 a. T\'f4i m\u7903  c\u7917 a r\u7891 i, h\u7855 n nh\u7853 n ra kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7895  \u7903  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh li\u7873 n s\u7869  \u273 i ngay. N\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c g\'f5 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y em l\'e0m sao ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y an t\'e2m m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\u432 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n n\u7857 m s\u7845 p d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\'e1ch m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng n\u7873 n nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec, l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong l\'f2ng s\u7907  h\'e3i, ngay c\u7843  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u7903  l\u7841 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m. C\u7853 u ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "... V\u7853 y em v\u7899 i anh c\'f9ng \u273 i."\cb1 \
