\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c l\u432 u lo\'e1t d\'f9ng ch\u259 n bao c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, b\'e2y gi\u7901  em c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i c\'f9ng t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn nh\'ecn m\'ecnh nh\uc0\u432  c\'e1i b\'e1nh \'fa \u7889 ng tr\'fac: "... Th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec em \u273 i ki\u7875 u g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mu\u7889 n \'f4m c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\u7843 i gi\'e3y ch\u259 n ra ph\u7911  th\'eam \'e1o kho\'e1c \u273 i theo sau Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'fac \uc0\u273 \'f3 ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a l\u7841 i k\'e9o d\'e0i \'edt nh\u7845 t n\u259 m ph\'fat, tuy r\u7857 ng v\u7851 n l\'e0 lo\u7841 i t\u7847 n su\u7845 t kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m qu\u7927  d\u7883  kia, nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau qu\u7843  th\u7921 c tim l\u7899 n, kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y cho d\'f9 c\'f3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 qu\u7927 , c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh nh\'e0 m\'ecnh \'e9p ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i theo ph\'eda sau Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\'ecn h\u7855 n m\u7903  c\u7917 a, ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a t\u7889 i \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 b\'f3ng \u273 \'e8n m\'e0u v\'e0ng treo \u7903  ch\u7895  c\u7893 ng l\u7899 n ngo\'e0i s\'e2n ph\'e1t ra \'e1nh s\'e1ng m\u7901  m\u7901 , qu\u7843  nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i: "T\'f4i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai m\'e0, em c\'f2n kh\'f4ng tin. Ch\u7855 c l\'e0 \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t g\'ec \u273 \'f3 khua c\u7917 a m\u7899 i ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, v\u7915 a nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i li\u7873 n ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7871 t h\u7907 p v\u7899 i \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u v\u7915 a r\u7891 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i c\'f3 l\'fd, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i v\'ec kinh h\'e3i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7907 ng ng\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 nh\u7919 ng g\'ec c\u7853 u th\u7845 y ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7875  cho c\u7853 u th\u7845 y, c\'f3 v\'e0i th\u7913  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u7889  \'fd che l\u7845 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ed d\uc0\u7909  nh\u432  "C\'f4 g\'e1i" \u273 \u7913 ng tr\'ean c\u7847 u thang s\u7855 t m\'e0u xanh ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a, to\'e0n th\'e2n \u432 \u7899 t s\u361 ng, t\'f3c d\'e0i r\u361  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7855 t c\'e1 ch\'e2n. Tr\'f2ng m\u7855 t m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng v\'f4 th\u7847 n c\u7911 a n\'f3 o\'e1n \u273 \u7897 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\'f2ng ch\u7885 c, hai h\u7889 c m\u7855 t ch\u7843 y ra huy\u7871 t l\u7879  kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng, ph\'eda sau n\'f3 c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en x\u7845 p x\u7881  h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i lay \u273 \u7897 ng, ph\u7847 n "M\u7863 t" to\'e1t ra bi\u7875 u t\'ecnh v\u7863 n v\u7865 o th\u7889 ng kh\u7893 , t\u7921 a h\u7891  v\'f4 thanh k\'eau r\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t b\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, m\u7897 t b\'ean \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, \u273 em t\u7845 t c\u7843  ng\u259 n c\'e1ch ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a, nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng nh\u7871 ch l\'ean m\u7897 t \u273 \u7897  cong t\'e0 l\u7879  ch\'e2m ch\u7885 c.\cb1 \

