\cb3 M\uc0\u7845 y th\u7913  kia mu\u7889 n k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i l\u7845 p h\u7891 ... Th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0, to gan l\u7899 n m\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "K\'e9t ...c\uc0\u7841 ch" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\u7917 a \u273 \'e3 kh\'f3a, qu\u7927  \u7843 nh lay \u273 \u7897 ng kia c\u361 ng \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y n\u7919 a, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay v\'f4 h\'ecnh b\'f3p n\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y g\'e1nh n\u7863 ng trong l\'f2ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7843 i tr\u7915 , lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7883  nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m k\u7923  qu\'e1i n\'e0y \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u7853 u m\u417  h\u7891  c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c, th\u7913  v\u7889 n n\u7857 m s\u7845 p d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tinh th\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  li\u7873 n d\'e2ng l\'ean, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7849 y \u273 \u7849 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang mu\u7889 n \'f4m ch\u7863 t m\'ecnh: "\u272 \u7915 ng nh\'e1o n\u7919 a, s\'e1ng mai c\'f2n ph\u7843 i l\'e1i xe quay v\u7873  \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng nh\'e1o, ch\uc0\u7881  \'f4m em ng\u7911 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng th\'edch, kh\'f4ng tho\uc0\u7843 i m\'e1i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i xong quay ng\u432 \u7901 i qua, ch\u7881  \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i c\'e1i l\u432 ng cho h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... Qua c\uc0\u7847 u r\'fat v\'e1n." L\'fac s\u7907  h\'e3i th\'ec \'f4m h\u7855 n th\u7855 m thi\u7871 t nh\u432  g\'ec, d\'f9ng xong m\u7897 t c\'e1i li\u7873 n n\'e9m sang m\u7897 t b\'ean ch\u7859 ng th\'e8m ng\'f3 ng\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'e2\u803 m h\u432 \u803 c \'f4m m\u7897 t g\'f3c ch\u259 n, lui l\u7841 i m\u7897 t b\'ean, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7911  r\u7891 i m\u7899 i du\u7895 i hai tay ra nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\u7919 ng \u273 \'eam tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u244 \u768  ng\u244 \u769 c, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\'f4i c\u7889  \'fd, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m t\'f4i \'f4m em, l\'e0m sao em c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y ngh\uc0\u7881  v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n lu\'f4n ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i, ng\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 i l\'e0m l\u7841 i, t\u7893  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7921 c t\u7853 p sinh m\u7899 i \u273 \u7871 n, ng\u7891 i \u7903  ch\u7895  tr\u7889 ng ph\'eda sau c\u7853 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7851 n c\u7853 u ta \u273 i ph\'f2ng IT nh\u7853 n m\'e1y t\'ednh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 i ca b\u7897  ph\u7853 n k\u7929  thu\u7853 t \u273 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n phi\u7871 m v\u7899 i \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p trong ph\'f2ng, n\'f3i s\'e1ng s\u7899 m ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\'f2n \u273 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n th\u7883  tr\u7845 n C\u7893  M\u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bu\uc0\u7897 t mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "Tr\u432 \u417 ng ca anh c\u361 ng \u273 i du l\u7883 ch sao? M\u7845 y ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i em c\u361 ng \u273 i th\u7883  tr\u7845 n C\u7893  M\u7897 c \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 i ca m\u7897 t b\'ean d\u7885 n m\'e1y t\'ednh m\u7897 t b\'ean tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "H\u7847 y, \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3i n\u7919 a, du l\u7883 ch c\'e1i g\'ec ch\u7913 . Ch\u7891 ng em g\'e1i t\'f4i \u273 i c\'f4ng t\'e1c, con b\'e9 mang hai \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  \u273 i ch\u417 i, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  khuya ng\'e0y h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho t\'f4i n\'f3i l\'e0 ch\'e1u t\'f4i \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i t\'e0 r\u7891 i, k\'eau t\'f4i \u273 i \u273 \'f3n b\u7885 n h\u7885 . T\'f4i nghe con b\'e9 n\'f3i m\u417  m\u417  h\u7891  h\u7891 , s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c s\'e1ng s\u7899 m h\'f4m sau l\u7853 p t\u7913 c kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'f3n b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\'f3i: "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean \u273 i ch\'f9a chi\u7873 n \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n c\'e1c loa\u803 i sao? Th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng? \u7902  \u273 \'e2u linh nghi\u7879 m nh\u7845 t, \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i b\u7843 o em g\'e1i t\'f4i \u273 \u432 a m\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  \u273 i xem. Lo\u7841 i v\u7853 t n\'e0y *kh\'f4ng s\u7907  nh\u7845 t v\u7841 n ch\u7881  s\u7907  v\u7841 n nh\u7845 t, tuy n\'f3i l\'e0 kh\'f4ng tin nh\u432 ng tim v\u7851 n treo ng\u432 \u7907 c v\'ec s\u7907 , c\u7913  \u273 i xem th\u7917  c\u7847 u an t\'e2m."\cb1 \
