\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7917 ng s\u7889 t, c\u432 \u7901 i: "Tr\u432 \u417 ng ca anh nghe ai n\'f3i v\u7853 y? Em c\'f3 bao gi\u7901  tin nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \'e2u, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia \u273 i \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n ch\'f9a mi\u7871 u c\u361 ng l\'e0 v\'ec \u273 i c\'f9ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i th\'f4i." Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u n\'f3i t\u7899 i th\u7883  tr\u7845 n C\u7893  M\u7897 c, ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m l\'e0 l\u7841 , v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a li\'ean t\u7909 c hai ng\'e0y, tuy r\u7857 ng Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i l\'e0 \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t n\'e0o \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng l\u7855 m, may m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  v\u7873 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec x\u7843 y ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i m\u7863 t tr\'f2n \u273 i t\u7899 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh tr\'eau ch\u7885 c n\'f3i: "Tr\u432 \u417 ng ca anh \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec, ti\u7875 u t\u7917  n\'e0y t\u7915  khi y\'eau v\'e0o \u273 \'e3 ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a duy v\u7853 t r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao c\uc0\u361 ng \u273 ang trong th\u7901 i gian l\'e0m vi\u7879 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi nh\u7853 n m\'e1y t\'ednh xong li\u7873 n t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i c\'f9ng th\u7921 c t\u7853 p sinh tr\u7903  v\u7873 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n t\'e1n d\'f3c n\'e0y trong l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\u7853 y cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng y\'ean \u7893 n tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  th\u7901 i ti\u7871 t n\'f3ng l\'ean t\u7915 ng ng\'e0y, c\'f2n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\u7907 n s\'f3ng n\'e0o n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t h\'f4m th\u7913  s\'e1u n\u7885 , g\u7847 n t\u7899 i l\'fac tan l\'e0m Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean th\'e8m \u259 n t\'f4m cay. C\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u432 \u7899 c kia Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng l\'e0m c\u417 m, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 \u273 i\u7875 m th\u7847 n b\'ed c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean n\u7845 u c\u417 m \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m r\u7845 t ngon, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\'f4ng th\u7913 c tr\'ean m\u7841 ng l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Mu\u7889 n \u259 n t\'f4m cay."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qua ch\uc0\u7915 ng m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7885 i l\u7841 i \u273 \'fang l\'fac c\u7853 u tan vi\u7879 c, c\'e1ch s\'f3ng \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\'f3 v\u7867  tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897 ng l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i h\u7887 i: "Th\u7871  n\'e0o l\u7841 i th\'e8m c\'e1i \u273 \'f3? T\'f4i g\u7917 i nguy\'ean li\u7879 u c\u7847 n cho em, em \u273 i mua nh\'e9, nh\u7899  ph\u7843 i mua t\'f4m t\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean mua cho h\u7855 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7899  l\'e0 h\'ecnh nh\u432  th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7899 i \u7903  b\'ean nhau ch\u432 a l\'e2u, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i di \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 h\u7887 ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o \u273 \u7875  li\'ean l\u7841 c, ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau c\u7853 u li\u7873 n \u273 i mua v\u7873  m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c lo\u7841 i m\u7899 i nh\u7845 t c\'f9ng h\'e3ng v\u7899 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7863 t n\'f3ng r\u7847 n l\'ean: "Sao c\'f2n g\u7885 i l\u7841 i cho em l\'e0m g\'ec? G\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n cho em gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  b\'ean kia \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i tr\u7847 m tr\u7847 m n\'f3i: "Mu\u7889 n nghe gi\u7885 ng em."\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 t\'ecnh tho\uc0\u7841 i c\u361  r\'edch, m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t v\u7851 n n\'f3ng l\'ean. C\u7853 u v\u7897 i v\'e0ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng "Y\'ean t\'e2m em s\u7869  mua", xong li\u7873 n c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7841 i ca \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p \u7903  b\'ean ph\u7843 i \u273 ang thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c chu\u7849 n b\u7883  v\u7873  nh\'e0 tr\'eau gh\u7865 o li\u7871 c c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Tu\u7893 i tr\u7867  th\u7853 t l\'e0 t\u7889 t nha. Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec nhanh nhanh thu d\u7885 n \u273 i th\'f4i, \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7875  b\u7841 n g\'e1i s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t ch\u7901 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i b\u7919 a c\u417 m n\'e0y l\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7891  cay, h\u7843 i s\u7843 n, \u259 n qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u, n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y d\u7841  d\'e0y s\'f4i tr\'e0o, \u273 au qu\u7863 n, kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7871 n l\u7907 i h\u7841 i, n\'f4n \u7885 e \u273 \u7871 n m\u7855 t c\u361 ng \u273 \u7887  l\'ean, nh\'ecn qua n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t l\u432 ng tr\'f2ng, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \'f3i ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch, tr\'ean tr\'e1n th\u7845 m m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7841 nh, th\'e2n th\u7875  run run t\u7915 ng tr\u7853 n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i ngay c\u7843  n\'f3i c\u361 ng n\'f3i kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7889  g\u7855 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "... Ngh\'eanh Chi, d\'ecu em xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u, \u273 \u432 a em \u273 i b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch, h\u7855 n \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ch\u7895  t\u7889 i c\u7841 nh c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m, th\u7847 n s\u7855 c t\u7889 i t\u259 m kh\'f3 ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u432  duy c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p, m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'ecnh nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883 , l\'e0 \u273 i theo m\'ecnh t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ra kh\u7887 i c\u7917 a, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2u ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec v\uc0\u7853 y l\u7841 i c\u7889  s\u7913 c b\u7893  sung m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "... G\u7885 i taxi n\'f3i \u273 i b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n \u272 \u7879  Tam l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c." B\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n \u272 \u7879  Tam l\'e0 b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n ch\'ednh quy g\u7847 n nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i t\u7899 i \u273 \u7905  l\u7845 y c\u7853 u, \u273 em ng\u432 \u7901 i \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, \u273 \u432 a tay l\u7845 y m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c kh\u259 n m\u7863 t xu\u7889 ng lau m\u7863 t cho c\u7853 u. Tay ph\u7843 i \'f4m c\u7853 u, tay tr\'e1i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng xoa m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i gh\'e9 v\'e0o b\'ean tai c\u7853 u nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean em ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c, ngoan, t\u7881 nh ng\u7911  ch\'fang ta \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 n r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  th\'f4i mi\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tuy r\u7857 ng v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\'e2n th\u7875  kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u v\'f4 c\'f9ng, nh\u432 ng \'fd th\u7913 c l\u7841 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n m\'ea man, sau khi Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7915 a d\u7913 t d\u7901 i li\u7873 n l\'e2m v\'e0o gi\u7845 c ng\u7911  s\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i, t\u7855 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \'e8n trong nh\'e0, \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i \u7903  tr\'ean s\'f4 pha ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, \'e1nh tr\u259 ng t\u7915  c\u7917 a s\u7893  chi\u7871 u v\'e0o r\u417 i tr\'ean g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, chi\u7871 u ra m\u7897 t m\u7843 nh t\'e1i nh\u7907 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7913 a ng\u244 \u769 c. H\u7855 n ch\u7841 m nh\u7865  l\'ean l\'f4ng m\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'fac ng\u7911  m\u417  v\u7851 n v\'ec kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u m\'e0 nh\u259 n l\u7841 i, c\'f3 ch\'fat \u273 au l\'f2ng, l\u7841 i h\'f4n l\'ean.\cb1 \
