\cb3 Khi t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 ang \u7903  nh\'e0, \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n t\u7915  \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  chi\u7871 u v\'e0o l\'e0 ngu\u7891 n s\'e1ng duy nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong c\uc0\u259 n ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n \u273 \u7863 t hai chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng b\u7879 nh, \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7875  khung s\u7855 t truy\u7873 n d\u7883 ch, nh\'ecn c\'e1ch s\u7855 p x\u7871 p b\'e0i tr\'ed th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 trong vi\u7879 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nghi ng\u7901 , b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 ang n\u7857 m chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng ph\'eda trong, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u h\u417 i y\'ean t\u297 nh qu\'e1 m\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7847 n d\u7847 n th\'edch \u7913 ng v\u7899 i b\'f3ng t\u7889 i trong ph\'f2ng, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra tr\'ean chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n ph\'eda ngo\'e0i kia c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang ng\u7891 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  kh\'f4ng h\u7873  nh\'fac nh\'edch, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t ra \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh g\'ec, b\u7903 i v\u7853 y l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'ea\u777  \'fd \u273 \u234 \u769 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd th\uc0\u7913 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u432 a t\u7881 nh t\'e1o h\u7859 n, th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng k\'eau l\'ean: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, Ngh\'eanh Chi?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'f3ng ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kia nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng k\'eau ch\u7853 m r\'e3i xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec \u273 \'f3, Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7855 n c\'f3 g\u7847 y nh\u432  v\u7853 y sao? H\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7845 p nh\u432  v\u7853 y sao? M\u7845 u ch\u7889 t nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0... h\u7855 n \u273 \'e2u c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7847 u t\'f3c d\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en kia...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn th\u7913  kia quay l\u7841 i ch\'ednh di\u7879 n, c\u361 ng m\u7863 c k\u7879  n\u417 i n\'e0y l\'e0 b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n m\'e0 l\'fac n\'e0y l\'e0 \u273 \'eam khuya, ch\u7881  nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i g\'e0o l\u7899 n: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi!" \u272 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i tay ph\u7843 i v\'f4 th\u7913 c n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho d\'f9 \uc0\u273 ang trong s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7921 c \u273 \u7897 , c\u7853 u v\u7851 n v\'ec th\u7871  m\'e0 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh\'97\'97b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  n\'e0y l\'e0 t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u ra? B\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 mang th\'e0nh th\'f3i quen v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ch\'fa \'fd \u273 \u7871 n. C\u7853 u r\'f5 r\'e0ng nh\u7899  th\u7913  m\'ecnh \u273 eo l\'e0 ng\u7885 c m\'e0 b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u432 a...\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7917 a kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng b\u7883  \u273 \'e1 v\u259 ng ra, \u273 \u7853 p v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng vang nh\u7887 . G\u7847 n nh\u432  trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t ti\u7871 p theo \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i tay quen thu\u7897 c \'f4m l\u7845 y \u7845 n v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y thanh \'e2m c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "A Di\'ean, l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? Em m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra nh\'ecn t\'f4i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7899 i d\'e1m m\u7903  m\u7855 t, ch\u7881  v\'e0o chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh kia, gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7851 n c\'f2n run r\u7849 y: "Ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 'Ng\u432 \u7901 i' ng\u7891 i ..."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u b\u7845 t an m\'e0 nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, ng\u7909  \'fd \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng \'97\'97 c\u7853 u \u273 ang \'e1m ch\u7881  c\'e1i kia kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7901  l\'ean t\'f3c mai th\u7845 m \u432 \u7899 t m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7841 nh b\u7883  nh\'e1y m\u7855 t kia k\'edch ra, hai m\u7855 t t\u7889 i s\u7847 m l\u7841 i, m\u7873 m gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7887  gi\u7885 ng "\u7914 " m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\'f3 ch\'fat t\u7911 i th\'e2n: "Anh \u273 i \u273 \'e2u th\u7871 ? Sao kh\'f4ng b\u7891 i em?" N\'f3i xong ch\'ednh m\'ecnh c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'ecnh kh\'e1c ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh qu\u7843  th\u7921 c gi\u7889 ng m\'f4\u803 t c\'f4 b\'e9 m\u432 \u7901 i tu\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i, \u7845 n c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, \'f4m ch\u7863 t h\u417 n n\u7919 a: "T\'f4i \u273 i l\'e0m th\u7911  t\u7909 c n\u7857 m vi\u7879 n v\u7899 i t\'ecm b\'e1c s\u297  cho em."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao t\'f4i c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  r\u7901 i \u273 i ch\u7913 , kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\'f4i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh em \u432 ?" Tay h\u7855 n t\u7915  tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7841  xu\u7889 ng, l\'e0m nh\u432  v\'f4 t\'ecnh \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean ch\u7895  b\'ecnh s\u7913  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u \u273 \'f3 c\u7911 a h\u7855 n: "Ph\u7843 i n\u7857 m vi\u7879 n sao? L\'e0 b\u7879 nh g\'ec v\u7853 y? C\'f3 nghi\'eam tr\u7885 ng kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng sao," Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7905  c\u7853 u n\u7857 m l\u7841 i l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, d\'e9m ch\u259 n c\u7849 n th\u7853 n cho c\u7853 u, "Vi\'eam d\u7841  d\'e0y c\u7845 p t\'ednh, t\u7889 i nay \u7903  l\u7841 i truy\u7873 n d\u7883 ch m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m mai l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  v\u7873  nh\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat b\uc0\u7845 t an li\u7871 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn gi\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh: "... \u272 \u7893 i ph\'f2ng kh\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 ph\'f2ng tr\u7889 ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng r\u7891 i. Kh\'f4ng sao \u273 \'e2u, l\u7847 n n\'e0y t\'f4i s\u7869  \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh tr\'f4ng coi em, m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 i, \u273 \u7875  em lu\'f4n nh\'ecn th\u7845 y t\'f4i, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe k\u7875  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n k\u7923  qu\'e1i \u7903  b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n, nh\u432 ng t\u7853 n m\u7855 t nh\'ecn th\u7845 y th\'ec \u7903  trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean. Nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao c\u7853 u l\u7841 i tin c\u7853 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u7903  c\'f9ng h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n s\u7907  nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  qu\u7927  qu\u7927  qu\'e1i qu\'e1i \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7865  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  s\u7907  h\u7855 n ch\u7841 y m\u7845 t m\'e0 gi\u7919  ch\u7863 t tay tr\'e1i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \'e8 \u7903  trong ch\u259 n kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng. Ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean, \'e1nh m\u7855 t nh\'ecn \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u7871 t s\u7913 c v\'f4 t\u7897 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  k\u7867  tr\u7897 m m\u7897 t tay c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7855 m l\u7841 i tay c\u7853 u th\u7853 t ch\u7863 t, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "Ng\u7911  \u273 i, l\'e1t n\u7919 a ng\u432 \u7901 i truy\u7873 n d\u7883 ch s\u7869  t\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i ngh\u297  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n, nh\'e2ng cao ng\u7921 c c\u7847 m l\u7845 y b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c \u273 \u432 a cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, anh c\'f3 nh\u7899  em b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u mang c\'e1i n\'e0y t\u7915  khi n\'e0o kh\'f4ng? Sao em l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng g\'ec nh\u7881 ? Ng\u7885 c b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i cho em \u273 \'e2u r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u417 i h\u417 i nheo l\u7841 i, c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "Sao em l\u7841 i qu\'ean r\u7891 i, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 l\'fac hai ta m\u7899 i quen nhau n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i t\u7863 ng cho em m\'e0. Ng\u7885 c b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u432 a cho em kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i em ti\u7871 c n\'ean \u273 \'e3 c\u7845 t trong ng\u259 n k\'e9o d\u432 \u7899 i t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean "A..." m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\'f3 ch\'fat nghi ho\u7863 c t\u7841 i sao b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fat \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng n\'e0o v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7863 ng b\'ecnh s\u7913  cho m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c xo\u7855 n xu\'fdt, th\'e0nh th\u7853 t nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e2u l\u7855 m, trong l\'fac n\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \'e8n trong ph\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7903  l\'ean, m\u7897 t h\u7897  s\u297  gi\'fap c\u7855 m b\'ecnh truy\u7873 n d\u7883 ch ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7849 y \u273 \u7849 y c\u7853 u, d\u7895  d\'e0nh n\'f3i: "N\'e0o, A Di\'ean, du\u7895 i tay ra n\'e0o."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng \u273 \u432 a tay ra, h\u7897  s\u297  kia l\u432 u lo\'e1t hai ba c\'e1i c\u7855 m kim treo b\'ecnh cho c\u7853 u, to\'e0n b\u7897  qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e2u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\'f4, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec l\u7841 , nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng c\u7913 ng nh\u7855 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fat bi\u7875 u t\'ecnh n\'e0o, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  con r\u7889 i b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7847 u m\u7899 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\'f2n s\u7907  h\u7871 t h\u7891 n, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng li\u7873 n th\u7843  l\u7887 ng, n\u7871 u m\'ecnh c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i t\u259 ng ca c\u7843  \u273 \'eam ch\u259 m s\'f3c c\'e1c lo\u7841 i b\u7879 nh nh\'e2n, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng s\u7869  m\u7879 t \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng b\'e0y ra n\u7893 i bi\u7875 u t\'ecnh g\'ec th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e8n \u7889 ng tr\'ean tr\u7847 n nh\'e0 ph\'e1t ra \'e1nh s\'e1ng h\u417 i ch\'f3i m\u7855 t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u432 \u417 n tay ra che l\'ean m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, \'f4n h\'f2a n\'f3i: "Ng\u7911  \u273 i, ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u7919 a l\'e0 t\u7889 t r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7897  s\u297  \u273 \u7849 y xe r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, c\u7917 a "C\u7841 ch" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i, c\u259 n ph\'f2ng m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a l\'e2m v\'e0o trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ean c\uc0\u7841 nh c\'f3 m\u7897 t gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qua \u273 \'f3 ng\u7911 . C\u7853 u d\u7883 ch ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7873  ph\'eda gi\'e1 truy\u7873 n d\u7883 ch, v\u7895  v\u7895  n\u7917 a chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7889 ng: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, l\'ean \u273 \'e2y ng\u7911 , ch\'fang ta chen m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e8 tay c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng: "C\u7849 n th\u7853 n \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7909 ng v\'e0o." Nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7915  ch\u7889 i, thu\u7853 n theo l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7857 m l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, tay kho\'e1c l\'ean ngang h\'f4ng c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u7911  \u273 i, t\'f4i tr\'f4ng chai truy\u7873 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean mu\uc0\u7889 n \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau m\u7897 t c\'e2u, nh\u432 ng bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  l\u7841 i k\'e9o t\u7899 i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, m\'ed m\u7855 t n\u7863 ng n\u7873  h\u7841  xu\u7889 ng, \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \'e3 l\'e2m v\'e0o trong m\u7897 ng \u273 \u7865 p ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
