\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 c\u7843 m \u7913 ng b\u432 ng m\u7897 t ch\'e9n ch\'e1o ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n, \u273 \u7905  c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y: "D\u7841  d\'e0y em kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, hai ng\'e0y n\'e0y ch\u7881  cho ph\'e9p \u259 n ch\'e1o."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean u\uc0\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m ch\'e1o tr\'ean tay \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, ch\'fang ta tr\u7903  v\u7873  l\'fac n\'e0o? \u272 i v\u7873  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i: "Sau khi truy\u7873 n d\u7883 ch xong, v\'ec \u273 \u7875  cho b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n d\u7885 n gi\u432 \u7901 ng cho n\'ean quay v\u7873 . C\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng l\'fac \u273 i h\'f4m qua, g\u7885 i taxi \u273 \u432 a em v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7921  nh\u7911  vi\u7879 c n\'e0y h\'ecnh nh\u432  kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang l\u7855 m?\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao anh kh\'f4ng g\uc0\u7885 i em d\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua b\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\u7845 t t\u7881 nh m\u7845 t \u273 i \'fd th\u7913 c, Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t \'f4m hay c\'f5ng hay d\'f9ng b\u7845 t k\u7923  c\'e1ch g\'ec \u273 \u432 a m\'ecnh l\'ean taxi t\u7899 i b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 truy\u7873 n d\u7883 ch xong m\'ecnh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 kh\u7887 e l\'ean kh\'f4ng \'edt, c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u7911  thi\u7871 p \u273 i ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng h\'f4n m\'ea, v\'ec sao Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng g\u7885 i m\'ecnh d\u7853 y c\'f9ng nhau v\u7873 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u361  m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng, l\u7841 i m\'fac m\u7897 t th\'eca ch\'e1o b\'ecnh t\u297 nh b\'f3n cho c\u7853 u: "H\'f4m qua trong thu\u7889 c c\'f3 th\'e0nh ph\u7847 n an th\u7847 n gi\u7843 m \u273 au, b\'e1c s\u297  n\'f3i t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t kh\'f4ng n\'ean \u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c em, t\'f4i b\u7871  em c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 n s\u7913 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ki\u7871 n th\u7913 c y h\u7885 c m\u7897 t ch\u7919  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, d\u297  nhi\'ean l\'e0 tin.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'e0i ng\'e0y ti\uc0\u7871 p theo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  ch\u7883 u n\u7845 u ch\'e1o cho c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7871 n th\u7913  hai thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a c\'f2n ng\u259 n kh\'f4ng cho c\u7853 u \u273 i l\'e0m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f3c kh\'f4ng ra n\uc0\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, ch\u7881  l\'e0 vi\'eam d\u7841  d\'e0y c\u7845 p t\'ednh th\'f4i m\'e0, anh kh\'f4ng cho em \u259 n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec th\'f4i, \u273 \u7915 ng kh\'f3a em l\u7841 i tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng t\u297 nh d\u432 \u7905 ng ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i th\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7897 t c\'e2u \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng t\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qua hai tu\uc0\u7847 n, sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883 , ra s\u7913 c ph\u7843 n \u273 \u7889 i, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\u7845 y th\'e2n m\'ecnh ra l\'e0m h\u7889 i l\u7897 , d\'f9ng m\u7885 i c\'e1ch \u273 \'fat l\'f3t, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 l\u7845 y l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c quy\u7873 n l\u7907 i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u259 n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n h\'fap ch\'e1o. Nh\u432 ng th\u7921 c \u273 \u417 n v\u7851 n l\u7845 y thanh \u273 a\u803 m l\'e0m ch\u7911 , qu\'e1 l\u7841 nh qu\'e1 n\'f3ng qu\'e1 cay qu\'e1 d\u7847 u t\u7845 t c\u7843  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p c\u7853 u \u273 \u7909 ng t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 l\uc0\u7921 c d\'f9ng chi\u7871 c \u273 \u361 a ch\u7885 c v\'e0o s\'fap rau c\u7843 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, anh coi em l\'e0 th\u7887  \u273 \u7875  nu\'f4i hay saooo?"\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'f5 r\'e0ng m\uc0\u7895 i ng\'e0y v\u7845 t v\u7843  \u273 i l\'e0m mua th\u7913 c \u259 n nu\'f4i gia \u273 \'ecnh \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 c\u7853 u! Nh\u432 ng v\u7853 n m\u7879 nh l\u7841 i lu\'f4n b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c n\u7855 m gi\u7919 !\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i s\u7901  s\u7901  tai c\u7853 u: "C\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m, ch\u7881  nu\'f4i em v\u7915 a tr\u7855 ng v\u7915 a m\u7873 m nh\u432  th\u7887  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 ."\cb1 \
