\cb3 B\uc0\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n \u272 \u7879  Tam ph\'f2ng 308 tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7891 n \u273 \u7841 i "Chuy\u7879 n ma qu\'e1i", v\u7873  sau l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\'eam m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n qu\'e1i d\u7883  n\u7919 a, n\'f3i l\'e0 m\'e0n h\'ecnh gi\'e1m s\'e1t h\'e0nh lang b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n hi\u7875 n th\u7883  m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\u7885  n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam l\'fac r\u7841 ng s\'e1ng, c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'e1c s\u297  tr\u7921 c ban \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u259 n ph\'f2ng 308 v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n l\'ean \u7903  trong \u273 \'f3 h\u7891 i l\'e2u, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 l\'e0m g\'ec, sau \u273 \'f3 t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n \u273 i ra. Sau khi h\u7855 n \u273 i ch\u7915 ng hai m\u432 \u417 i ph\'fat, l\u7841 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\u7883  h\u7897  s\u297  tr\u7921 c ban \u273 \u7849 y xe y t\u7871  \u273 i v\'e0o, c\u361 ng b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n l\'ean \u7903  trong \u273 \'f3 ch\u7915 ng n\u259 m ph\'fat m\u7899 i t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n \u273 i ra. Nh\u432 ng khi h\u7887 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i trong cu\u7897 c r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\u7841 i c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'e0 m\u7897 ng du.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe n\'f3i sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\'f2n kinh \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n c\u7843  vi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7903 ng, vi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7863 ng l\u7869  m\u7901 i cao nh\'e2n t\u7899 i nh\'ecn, cao nh\'e2n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y l\'e0 qu\u7927  th\u7847 n m\u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  gi\'fap xem b\u7879 nh, ch\u7859 ng nh\u7919 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'f2n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n t\u7889 t, c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'edch \'e2m \u273 \u7913 c, n\'f3i y b\'e1c s\u297  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7921 c t\'e0i tr\u7883  b\u7879 nh c\u7913 u ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'ean m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 sau l\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \'f3, \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i d\u7845 u t\'edch qu\u7927  d\u7883  b\u7883  \u273 \u7891 n l\'e0 "Chuy\u7879 n ma qu\'e1i" c\u7911 a c\u259 n ph\'f2ng 308 c\u361 ng bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u hi\u7871 u k\u7923 , th\'edch \u273 \u7891 n th\u7893 i lo\u7841 i tin \u273 \u7891 n ch\u7913 a s\u7855 c th\'e1i th\u7847 n b\'ed n\'e0y, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n th\'eam m\u7855 m th\'eam mu\u7889 i c\'e0ng n\'f3i c\'e0ng huy\u7873 n b\'ed. Nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e1ch b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n \u272 \u7879  Tam r\u7845 t g\u7847 n, trong l\'fac v\'f4 t\'ecnh c\u361 ng nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7857 m vi\u7879 n h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 \'edch x\'e1c l\'e0 th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c "Th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 ", may m\'e0 Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  l\u7841 i k\u7883 p th\u7901 i, sau \u273 \'f3 t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t sinh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe xong li\u7873 n th\'f4i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \u7903  trong l\'f2ng, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t gi\'e1c ra m\'ecnh ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i trong cu\u7897 c c\u7911 a chuy\u7879 n qu\'e1i d\u7883  \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\u7885  l\'fac tan l\'e0m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\u7843 o an \u273 ang ng\u259 n l\u7841 i m\u7897 t v\u7883  l\'e3o nh\'e2n \u273 ang n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3, n\'f3i l\'e0 l\'e3o nh\'e2n nh\u432 ng nh\'ecn k\u7929  th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 qu\'e1 gi\'e0, b\u7897  d\'e1ng n\u259 m s\'e1u ch\u7909 c tu\u7893 i, m\u7863 c m\u7897 t th\'e2n qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\u7843 i b\u7889  m\'e0u x\'e1m ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng r\u7845 t c\u361 , trong ng\u7921 c k\u7865 p m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c t\'fai da tr\'e2u, b\u7897  d\'e1ng c\'f3 v\u7867  r\u7845 t g\u7845 p g\'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'f2ng nhi\uc0\u7879 t t\'ecnh c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ph\'e1t t\'e1c, \u273 i t\u7899 i h\u7887 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 o an \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng c\'f4ng nh\'e2n vi\'ean ch\u7913 c nh\u432  c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t kh\'e1ch kh\'ed, gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'f3i v\u7883  l\'e3o nh\'e2n n\'e0y mu\u7889 n v\'e0o trong t\'f2a nh\'e0 t\'ecm n\u417 i photocopy, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 trong t\'f2a nh\'e0 \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ch\u7895  \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta l\'e0m vi\u7879 c, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841  \u273 i v\'e0o, n\'ean \u273 \'e3 ch\u7881  cho \'f4ng ch\u7895  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 qu\'e1n photo g\u7847 n nh\u7845 t, k\'eau \'f4ng \u273 i qua \u273 \'f3 t\'ecm th\u7917  xem, l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7899 i h\u7855 n \u273 ang ch\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng cho \'f4ng \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i ra ngo\'e0i kh\u7887 i t\'f2a cao \u7889 c \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\'e3 t\u432  l\u7899 n, mu\u7889 n sang \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec ph\u7843 i \u273 i qua c\u7847 u v\u432 \u7907 t ho\u7863 c h\u7847 m \u273 i b\u7897  d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean sang \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i xem h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n c\u361 ng ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, hu\u7889 ng chi c\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t n\u417 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o an ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t khu th\u432 \u417 ng m\u7841 i t\u7893 ng h\u7907 p, tuy r\u7857 ng s\u7847 m u\u7845 t, c\u7917 a h\'e0ng nhi\u234 \u768 u, nh\u432 ng ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\'e1n photo.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\'f4 th\u7913 c suy \u273 o\'e1n th\'e2n ph\u7853 n c\u7911 a v\u7883  l\'e3o nh\'e2n n\'e0y. \u272 \u417 n v\u7883  c\u361 ng g\u7847 n b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n \u272 \u7879  Tam, l\'e0 \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 t\u7915  n\'f4ng th\'f4n l\'ean \u273 \'e2y kh\'e1m b\u7879 nh hay sao? Mu\u7889 n photo b\u7879 nh \'e1n, ch\u7913 ng minh th\u432 ? V\u7853 y th\'ec sao kh\'f4ng \u273 i ra qu\'e1n xung quanh b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n, c\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 b\'ean ngo\'e0i b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n c\'f3 hai qu\'e1n photo r\u7845 t d\u7877  th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng \u273 \'e3 h\u417 n n\u259 m gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u, nh\u432 ng th\'e1ng b\u7843 y kh\'ed tr\u7901 i v\u7851 n n\'f3ng b\u7913 c v\'f4 c\'f9ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u l\'e3o nh\'e2n li\'ean t\u7909 c ch\u7843 y m\u7891  h\'f4i, nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 nu\'f4i m\'ecnh l\u7899 n, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean sinh l\'f2ng c\u7843 m th\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i \'f4ng: "B\'e1c \u417 i, con bi\u7871 t t\u7915  n\u417 i n\'e0y \u273 i b\u7897  n\u259 m ph\'fat s\u7869  c\'f3 m\u7897 t qu\'e1n photo, \u273 \u7875  con \u273 \u432 a b\'e1c qua \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  c\u7893 ng \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7871 n qu\'e1n in kia ph\u7843 i \u273 i xu\u7889 ng h\u7847 m \u273 i b\u7897 , l\u7841 i \u273 i ra t\u7915  m\u7897 t h\u7847 m \u273 i b\u7897  kh\'e1c, m\u7863 c d\'f9 c\'e1ch kh\'e1 g\u7847 n, nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, h\u417 n n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng d\u7877  th\u7845 y. S\u432 \u7901 n h\u7847 m ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \u259 n h\u7871 t, h\'f4m nay tan t\u7847 m s\u7899 m l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 i mua th\u7913 c \u259 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7913 t kho\'e1t ti\u7877 n Ph\u7853 t ti\u7877 n \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n T\'e2y, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p d\u7851 n ng\u432 \u7901 i qua \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o nh\'e2n c\uc0\u7921 c k\u7923  c\u7843 m k\'edch, li\'ean t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "Ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7889 t a, v\u7851 n c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7889 t l\u7855 m, c\'e1m \u417 n c\'e1m \u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i \u7903  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, l\'e3o nh\'e2n \u273 i ch\u7853 m h\u417 n m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c theo sau, l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec li\'ean t\u7909 c n\'f3i l\u7901 i c\u7843 m t\u7841 , l\'fac sau ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i tr\u7903  n\'ean tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'f4ng \u273 ang kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng d\'f2 x\'e9t m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e1 v\u7905  im l\u7863 ng, t\'ecm chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7875  n\'f3i: "B\'e1c \u417 i, sao b\'e1c l\u7841 i g\u7845 p g\'e1p v\u7853 y \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o nh\'e2n phun ra hai ch\uc0\u7919 : "C\u7913 u ng\u432 \u7901 i." Nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n li\'ean t\u7909 c \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  \'f4ng nh\'ecn \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ti\u7871 p l\u7901 i n\'e0y nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, ngh\u297  th\u7847 m qu\u7843  nhi\'ean l\'e0 \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 \u273 i kh\'e1m b\u7879 nh. Th\u7853 t v\u7845 t v\u7843  \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n qu\'e1n photo, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y \'f4ng m\u7903  chi\u7871 c t\'fai da tr\'e2u ra, l\u7845 y ra \u273 \u7891  v\u7853 t b\'ean trong \'97\'97 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 b\u7879 nh \'e1n, ch\u7913 ng minh th\u432 , m\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t x\u7845 p m\u7845 y th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 gi\u7889 ng ph\'f9 tri\u7879 n tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p b\'e1t qu\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o nh\'e2n n\'f3i v\uc0\u7899 i nh\'e2n vi\'ean qu\'e1n photo: "L\'e0m phi\u7873 n ng\'e0i m\u7895 i ki\u7875 u sao ch\'e9p n\u259 m t\u7901 , c\u7905  A4, m\u7897 t m\u7863 t l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c." Nh\'ecn qua r\u7845 t c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e2n vi\'ean qu\'e1n l\uc0\u7849 m b\u7849 m li\u7871 c nh\'ecn \'f4ng v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, c\u7847 m l\u7845 y \u273 i photo.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u361 ng nh\'ecn ra v\u7883  l\'e3o nh\'e2n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 \u273 i kh\'e1m b\u7879 nh, th\u7853 m ch\'ed \u7849 n \u7849 n c\'f3 ch\'fat h\u7889 i h\u7853 n \u273 \'e3 xen v\'e0o vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, \u273 ang mu\u7889 n th\u7915 a c\u417  c\'e1o t\u7915 , l\'e3o nh\'e2n kia sau khi nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7891 i l\'e2u, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean quay sang nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u: "Ti\u7875 u huynh \u273 \u7879 , c\'f3 c\'e2u n\'e0y kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ta c\'f3 n\'ean n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng, nh\u432 ng t\u7841 i sao c\u7853 u l\u7841 i mang tro c\u7889 t c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 quan h\u7879  g\'ec v\u7899 i m\'ecnh tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 mang tro c\uc0\u7889 t tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i? Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  c\'e2u n\'f3i n\'e0y l\'e0m cho kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i s\u7907  h\'e3i, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 ang n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p l\u7901 i, n\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e2u cho c\'f3 l\u7879 : "V\u7853 y b\'e1c \u7903  \u273 \'e2y photo \u273 i \u7841 , con \u273 i \u273 \'e2y." Quay ng\u432 \u7901 i li\u7873 n mu\u7889 n r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\'e3o nh\'e2n l\u7841 i g\u7885 i c\u7853 u l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7907 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat," \'f4ng n\'f3i, "Ta h\u7887 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u n\u7919 a, ti\u7875 u huynh \u273 \u7879  trong nh\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u7853 u hay sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7851 n n\u7841 i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u7841 ." Trong l\'f2ng \u273 \'e3 v\'f4 c\'f9ng h\u7889 i h\u7853 n chuy\u7879 n d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng cho l\'e3o \u273 \u7847 u k\u7923  qu\'e1i n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\u7915 ng nghe k\u7875  v\u7873  l\u7915 a \u273 \u7843 o h\u7887 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m c\u7899  \u273 \u7875  l\u7915 a b\'e1n ph\u7909  n\u7919  tr\u7867  em, nh\u432 ng m\u7909 c ti\'eau g\'e2y \'e1n c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng k\u7867  l\u7915 a \u273 \u7843 o b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ph\u7909  n\u7919  tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i m\u7897 t th\'e2n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7927  m\'ecnh tu\u7893 i tr\u7867  s\u7913 c l\u7899 n, t\'e2m \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng v\u7899 i t\'ednh c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c th\u7853 t ra kh\'f4ng m\u7841 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y c\u361 ng m\u417  h\u7891  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o nh\'e2n nghe ra \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'f2ng b\u7883  v\'e0 kh\'f4ng ki\'ean nh\u7851 n trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, th\u7903  d\'e0i, \u273 \u432 a m\u7897 t th\u7913  gi\u7889 ng t\u7845 m danh thi\u7871 p qua: "Ta kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n, nh\u432 ng s\u7907  ti\u7875 u huynh \u273 \u7879  c\u7853 u th\'e2n \u7903  trong h\u7885 a c\'f2n kh\'f4ng t\u7921  bi\u7871 t, c\u361 ng ch\u7881  mong kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 nh\u432  ta ngh\u297 . H\'f4m nay ta c\'f2n c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\u7845 p, ti\u7875 u huynh \u273 \u7879  t\u7921  c\u7853 u xem x\'e9t \u273 i, l\'fac n\'e0o th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n th\'ec h\'e3y t\u7899 i t\'ecm ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3ng l\'f2ng tho\'e1t th\'e2n, qua loa nh\uc0\u7853 n danh thi\u7871 p nh\'e9t v\'e0o trong t\'fai \'e1o r\u7891 i nhanh ch\'f3ng r\u7901 i \u273 i, kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i ph\'eda sau t\u7845 m danh thi\u7871 p c\'f2n d\'e1n m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9 tri\u7879 n nh\u7887  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7845 p th\'e0nh h\'ecnh tam gi\'e1c m\'e0u v\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7845 m Thanh T\'e2m ph\'f9 ch\'ednh th\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
