\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y, t\u7841 i m\u7897 t kh\u7855 c c\u7853 u nh\u7853 n t\u7845 m danh thi\u7871 p n\'e0y, c\'f3 t\u7915 ng lu\u7891 ng t\u7915 ng lu\u7891 ng kh\'ed \u273 en th\u7853 t nh\u7887  t\u7915  ng\'f3n gi\u7919 a c\u7911 a c\u7853 u b\u7883  ph\'f9 tri\u7879 n h\'fat \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o nh\'e2n nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y m\u7897 t m\'e0n n\'e0y, trong l\'f2ng bi\u7871 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 o\'e1n kh\'f4ng sai, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i n\u7885 , hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  ch\u7855 c h\u7859 n c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\'f9y ti\u7879 n \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7911 , c\'f3 m\u7897 t s\u7889  vi\u7879 c c\u7913  \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta t\u7921  m\'ecnh x\'e1c nh\u7853 n s\u7869  t\u7889 t h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'ed \u273 en kia... th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 l\u7869  so v\u7899 i t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh kh\'f3 ch\u417 i h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c g\'ec, ch\u7881  l\'e0 tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i m\u7901  m\u7883 t, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  d\'f9ng n\'e3o qu\'e1 \u273 \u7897 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 m Thanh T\'e2m ph\'f9 kia y\'ean l\u7863 ng cu\u7897 n l\u7841 i trong t\'fai \'e1o c\u7853 u, ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m t\u7915 ng ch\'fat t\u7915 ng ch\'fat h\u7845 p thu kh\'ed \u273 en, m\'e9p gi\u7845 y d\u7847 n d\u7847 n xo\u7855 n l\u7841 i nh\u432  s\u7907 i t\'f3c b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 t. R\u7889 t cu\u7897 c, trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7915 ng xe l\u7841 i, t\u7845 m ph\'f9 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7845 p th\'e0nh h\'ecnh tam gi\'e1c t\u7921 a nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i g\'e1nh n\u7863 ng m\'e0 b\u7889 c th\'e0nh m\u7897 t l\'e0n kh\'f3i xanh, l\u432 \u7907 n l\u7901  ti\'eau th\u7845 t. D\'f2ng kh\'ed \u273 en b\u7883  d\u7851 n ra c\'f2n th\u7915 a to\'e0n b\u7897  r\u7909 t v\u7873  l\u7841 i trong c\u417  th\u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c \'f4m \u273 \u7847 u r\'ean r\u7881  ra ti\u7871 ng, h\'ecnh \u7843 nh n\u7917 a th\u7853 t n\u7917 a gi\u7843  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e8n k\'e9o qu\'e2n bi\u7871 n \u7843 o h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n trong \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7853 u t\'ecm v\u7873  l\'e0 k\'fd \u7913 c tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh\'97\'97 cha m\u7865  \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t qua \u273 \u7901 i, tang l\u7877 , c\u7853 u m\u417  m\u417  h\u7891  h\u7891  m\'e0 nh\'ecn di \u7843 nh cha m\u7865 , c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng kh\'f3c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t nhi\u7873 u "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" s\u7855 c m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch v\u7867  m\u7863 t c\u7913 ng nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i k\'e9o c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" kia l\'e0 ai, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 , c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u273 i c\'f9ng b\u7885 n h\u7885 , ra s\u7913 c lui v\'e0o trong l\'f2ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i... \'d4ng b\'e0 ch\u7881  cho l\'e0 c\u7853 u l\'e0 th\u432 \u417 ng t\'e2m qu\'e1 \u273 \u7897 , \'f4n nhu m\'e0 bi th\u432 \u417 ng \'f4m c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u b\u7883  \u273 \u7849 y t\u7915  tr\'ean c\u7847 u thang c\u7917 a h\'e0ng xu\u7889 ng, th\u7847 n s\u7855 c lo s\u7907  c\u7911 a b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i sau khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y d\u7845 u b\'e0n tay kia; l\'e3o nh\'e2n t\u7921  tay \u273 eo linh ng\u7885 c cho c\u7853 u; c\'f9ng v\u7899 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng s\u417 n d\'e3 b\u7843 o \u273 \u7883 a, ch\'f9a chi\u7873 n \u273 \u7841 o qu\'e1n che ph\u7911  trong m\'e2y m\'f9 s\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f3i, nh\u7919 ng t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n di\u7879 n v\'f4 bi\u7875 u t\'ecnh m\'e0 c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng qu\u7923  l\u7841 y...\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\'e0 Th\u7847 n Ph\u7853 t k\'edn tr\u7901 i, kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t ai c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7913 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  sau c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 o nh\'e2n n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, \u7903  \u273 \'e2y ta c\'f3 m\u7897 t bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p, con c\'f3 mu\u7889 n th\u7917  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe kh\'e1ch ch\uc0\u7841 y trong b\'f3ng \u273 \'eam, ma qu\u7927  v\'e2y quanh ng\u432 \u7901 i... c\u7853 u th\u7845 y ch\'ednh m\'ecnh tr\'e2n tr\u7885 ng n\'e2ng b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  \u273 eo \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c...\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97 c\uc0\u7853 u l\'e0 t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 \'f3n h\u7855 n v\'e0o nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\'ecnh cung k\'ednh \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t t\u7845 m b\'e0i v\u7883  m\'e0u \u273 en l\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901 ; c\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\'ecnh gi\u417  m\u7897 t ch\'e9n r\u432 \u7907 u, h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'e0i v\u7883  kia n\'f3i: "... Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , n\u259 m t\u7899 i k\'ednh xin ng\'e0i chi\u7871 u c\u7889  nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 ... \u273 \u7871 n t\u7897 t c\'f9ng l\'e0 ai?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd th\uc0\u7913 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng thanh t\u7881 nh nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7901  trong l\'f2ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u c\'e0ng khu\u7871 ch \u273 \u7841 i c\'e0ng l\u7899 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u suy ngh\u297  kh\'f4ng xu\u7875 . Ch\'e2n c\u7853 u c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c theo th\'f3i quen \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda nh\'e0, n\u7897 i t\'e2m ng\u7853 p tr\'e0n lo s\u7907  nghi ho\u7863 c b\u7845 t an.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 i v\'e0o c\u7917 a \u273 \u417 n nguy\'ean, thang m\'e1y \u273 i m\u7895 i ng\'e0y gi\u7901  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t con c\u7921  th\'fa m\'e0u x\'e1m \u273 \u7853 m l\'e0m t\u7915  v\u7853 t li\u7879 u v\'f4 c\u417 , mu\u7889 n c\u7855 n nu\u7889 t c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong; la\u803 i nh\u432  m\u7897 t c\'e1nh c\u7893 ng l\u7899 n th\'f4ng v\u7899 i \u272 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c. V\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng ph\u7843 n quang l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o trong thang m\'e1y ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t t\'e1i nh\u7907 t \u432 \u7899 t m\u7891  h\'f4i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7841 nh \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 m \u273 \u7851 m \'e1o s\u417  mi \u273 \u417 n b\u7841 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\u7841 nh, v\u7853 y m\'e0 ch\u7847 n ch\u7901  kh\'f4ng b\u432 \u7899 c n\u7893 i. M\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi c\u7917 a thang m\'e1y \u273 \'f3ng m\u7903  ba l\u432 \u7907 t, b\'ean c\u7841 nh l\u7841 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i t\u7899 i c\u7853 u m\u7899 i c\'f9ng theo ti\u7871 n v\'e0o trong thang m\'e1y, nh\u7845 n s\u7889  t\u7847 ng quen thu\u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 nh\u7899  ra v\u7883  Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng kia, c\u7843  chuy\u7879 n \'f4ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7843 o m\'ecnh th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng b\'e0i v\u7883  v\'e0 \u273 eo b\'ecnh s\u7913  \u273 \u7921 ng tro c\u7889 t. B\'ecnh s\u7913  hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i v\u7851 n \u273 ang mang \u7903  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\'e0i v\u7883  kia \u273 \'e2u r\u7891 i? B\u7883  Ngh\'eanh Chi thu h\u7891 i? Ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 ai?\cb1 \
\cb3 ... B\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, v\'ec sao \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\u7841 i qu\'ean nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y l\'f2ng c\u7853 u ch\u7907 t l\u7841 nh, c\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 m\'ecnh b\u7883  vi\'eam d\u7841  d\'e0y c\u7845 p t\'ednh n\u7857 m vi\u7879 n, h\u7887 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  n\'e0y l\'e0 \u7903  \u273 \'e2u ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 G\uc0\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t t\u432 \u417 i c\u432 \u7901 i \'f4n nhu c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'f5 r\'e0ng ch\'ednh h\uc0\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, "\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac hai ta m\u7899 i quen t\'f4i t\u7863 ng cho em".\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 t\'f4i t\uc0\u7863 ng cho em.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  l\u7841 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 che \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t b\u7883  \u273 \u7849 y ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c th\u7845 y r\'f5 t\u7845 m b\'e0i v\u7883  m\'e0u \u273 en c\'f9ng d\'f2ng ch\u7919  m\'e0u v\'e0ng ph\'eda tr\'ean. Tr\'ean \u273 \'f3 vi\u7871 t, "Di\u7879 p th\u7883  Ngh\'eanh Chi chi linh" .\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \u7903  trong nh\'e2n sinh c\u7911 a c\u7853 u l\'e0 ai?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\'e0y qua ng\'e0y \u7903  chung, gi\'fap c\u7853 u trong l\'fac kh\'f3 kh\u259 n l\'e0 ai?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n h\'e0ng \uc0\u273 \'eam c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u273 \u7847 u g\u7889 i tay \u7845 p, tri\u7873 n mi\'ean hoan h\u7843 o th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 ai...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ngh\u297  ti\u7871 p n\u7919 a, l\'fac \'fd th\u7913 c l\u7841 i m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 v\'f4 th\u7913 c b\u432 \u7899 c ra kh\u7887 i thang m\'e1y, \u273 i t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'e1ch c\'e1ch" m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\u7917 a m\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n du\uc0\u7895 i m\u7897 t tay ra d\u7855 t c\u7853 u v\'e0o, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "H\'f4m nay l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? Ng\u7889 c r\u7891 i? Thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u259 n c\u417 m n\'e0o." D\u7913 t l\u7901 i l\u7841 i quay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i v\'e0o trong b\u7871 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong c\uc0\u259 n nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n t\u7887 a kh\u7855 p m\'f9i th\u7913 c \u259 n th\u417 m, c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng \u7845 m \'e1p t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng gi\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7903  ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i, tay gi\u7845 u sau l\u432 ng l\u7841 i run k\u7883 ch li\u7879 t h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u y\'ean l\u7863 ng \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda t\u7911  tivi, c\u7847 m chi\u7871 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\'ecnh mua cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'ean, g\'f5 sinh nh\u7853 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'e0o gi\u7843 i kh\'f3a, v\u7915 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\'e0n h\'ecnh hi\u7879 n l\'ean nh\'e3n hi\u7879 u c\u7911 a nh\'e0 s\u7843 n xu\u7845 t, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c t\u7855 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, l\u432 u lo\'e1t m\u7903  n\u7855 p ph\'eda sau ra \'97\'97 n\u417 i v\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  l\u7855 p sim, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 ai, d\'f9ng m\uc0\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 sim, li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i c\u7853 u h\u417 n n\u7917 a n\u259 m qua?\cb1 \
\cb3 Hay l\'e0 h\uc0\u7855 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i...\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n \uc0\u273 \'e3 b\u432 ng \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 i ra, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng ng\'e0y g\u7885 i c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean, x\u7899 i c\u417 m n\'e0o. Sao em v\u7851 n ch\u432 a thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o? Hay l\'e0 ch\u7901  t\'f4i t\u7921  tay thay cho em?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, l\u7855 p l\u7841 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o, tay v\u7899 i v\'e0o trong t\'fai \'e1o, run r\u7849 y s\u7901  l\'ean t\u7845 m danh thi\u7871 p l\'e3o nh\'e2n kia \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i cho m\'ecnh, sau \u273 \'f3 n\u7895  l\u7921 c gi\u7919  th\u7847 n s\u7855 c nh\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7847 m qu\u7847 n \'e1o treo l\'ean, thay \u273 \u7891  m\u7863 c \u7903  nh\'e0. C\u7853 u suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, l\u7845 y linh ng\u7885 c trong t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng ra, n\u7855 m trong l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 x\u7899 i c\u417 m xong, ng\u7891 i \u7903  tr\'ean b\'e0n c\u417 m ch\u7901  c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn khung c\uc0\u7843 nh quen thu\u7897 c, do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7855 n r\u259 ng, \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda nam "nh\'e2n", nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \'f4m l\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\u7921 a \u273 \u7847 u v\'f9i v\'e0o ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i s\u7901  s\u7901  t\'f3c c\u7853 u: "H\'f4m nay l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? Y\u7871 u \u7899 t th\u7871  n\'e0y? Nh\u7899  t\'f4i \u432 ? \u7902  b\'ean ngo\'e0i b\u7883  oan \u7913 c?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \uc0\u273 \u7897  \u7845 m, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nh\u7883 p tim. H\u7871 t th\u7843 y trong qu\'e1 kh\u7913 , qu\u7843  nhi\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n gi\u7843  l\u7915 a ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t d\'f2ng kh\'ed \u273 en cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7845 n v\'edt trong l\'f2ng r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c tan h\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7901  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng xem nh\u7865 , gi\u7901  ph\'fat n\'e0y t\u7915 ng c\'e1i m\u7897 t b\u7883  ph\'f3ng \u273 \u7841 i, tr\u7903  n\'ean v\'f4 c\'f9ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau kh\'f4ng r\'f5 lai l\u7883 ch \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n trong cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c kh\'f4ng ra kh\u7887 i c\u7917 a th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i \u259 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0... ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\'ecnh c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y\'97\'97 c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 thu\u7853 t che m\u7855 t thu\u7853 t m\'ea t\'e2m, ma m\'ea qu\u7927  \'e1m m\'e0 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n th\uc0\u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u run r\u7849 y, trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n cu\u7891 ng lo\u7841 n tr\'e1nh ra kh\u7887 i \'f4m \u226 \u769 p n\'e0y, c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 ch\u7841 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\'edu m\'e0y m\u7897 t c\'e1i, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, ch\u7881  \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c c\'e0ng ch\u7863 t h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7849 n th\u7853 n ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn ph\u7847 n da c\u7893  l\u7897  ra c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 e m\u7841 nh mang theo t\u7917  kh\'ed, c\u361 ng may, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7871 t l\u7889 m \u273 \u7889 m c\u7911 a thi th\u7875 . C\u7853 u ngh\u297  t\u7899 i b\'ecnh s\u7913  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh, c\u361 ng l\'e0 tro c\u7889 t c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y v\u7851 n lu\'f4n mang tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, th\'e2n th\u7875  th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m kh\'f4ng c\'f2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quay m\u7863 t c\u7853 u l\'ean, n\u7909  h\'f4n m\u7873 m nh\u7865  r\u417 i tr\'ean m\'ed m\u7855 t nh\u7855 m l\u7841 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7844 m \'e1p ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \'e3 thay \u273 \u7893 i, c\u7853 u run r\u7849 y kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7893  h\u7885 ng cu\u7891 n cu\u7897 n, m\u7897 t c\'e2u mu\u7889 n d\'e2ng l\'ean m\u7845 y l\u7847 n, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i v\u7851 n nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , t\'f4i sai r\u7891 i, tha cho t\'f4i \u273 i..." Trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n c\u7847 u bu\'f4ng tha, mu\u7889 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c khoan dung, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i s\u7907  h\'e3i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i n\u7893 i m\u7897 t ch\u7919 . C\u7853 u s\u7907  h\'e3i l\'fac n\'e0y v\u7841 ch tr\u7847 n ra th\'ec to\'e0n b\u7897  s\u7869  k\u7871 t th\'fac. C\u7853 u th\'e0 r\u7857 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c l\u7915 a m\'ecnh d\u7889 i ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong m\uc0\u7897 t ng\'e0y cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n thi\'ean, m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n h\'f4m nay l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t x\u7865 t qua trong \u273 \u7847 u, t\u7845 m danh thi\u7871 p trong t\'fai \'e1o kia l\u7841 i th\'e0nh n\u417 i g\u7917 i g\u7855 m hy v\u7885 ng duy nh\u7845 t l\'fac n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y mai... kh\'f4ng n\'ean s\uc0\u7907 , kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7897  ra manh m\u7889 i... ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng qua h\'f4m nay l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ch\u7881  im l\u7863 ng t\u7915  t\u7915  nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, n\u7895  l\u7921 c kh\u7855 c ch\u7871  run r\u7849 y th\u7853 t nh\u7887  s\'e2u trong n\u7897 i t\'e2m kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kia, t\u7921 a nh\u432  hi\u7871 n t\u7871  th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n t\u7915 ng n\u7909  h\'f4n c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u7841  xu\u7889 ng tr\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u.\
