\cf2 \cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang h\'f4n, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \'f4m c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, \u273 i v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  n\'e9m l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u432 \u417 n tay mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng n\u7863 n ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7849 y "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t \u273 ang mu\u7889 n \'e1p xu\u7889 ng: "... Ngh\'eanh Chi, \u259 n c\u417 m tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e3, em \u273 \'f3i b\u7909 ng." C\u7853 u \'e9pbu\u7897 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u432 ng l\'f4ng mi v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng run r\u7849 y, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u432 \u417 m b\u432 \u7899 m b\u7883  qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u432 a th\u7887 a m\'e3n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e0m g\'ec bu\'f4ng c\u7853 u ra, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \'f4m l\u7845 y c\u7853 u, th\u7845 y c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n n\u7855 m quy\u7873 n, h\u7887 i: "A Di\'ean, trong tay em c\u7847 m g\'ec v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  tay ra, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "L\'e0 mi\u7871 ng ng\u7885 c b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i t\u7863 ng cho em, em mu\u7889 n cho anh."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, em \u273 eo cho t\'f4i nh\'e9?" N\'f3i xong ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, s\u7901  s\u7901  \u273 eo ng\u7885 c l\'ean c\u7893  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi\'97\'97 \u273 \'fang nh\u432  c\u7853 u \u273 o\'e1n, ng\u7885 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  c\u259 n b\u7843 n v\'f4 d\u7909 ng. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\'e0y ng\'e0y ng\u7911  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u, linh ng\u7885 c l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  \u7903  trong t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, n\u7871 u nh\u432  h\u7919 u d\u7909 ng, th\'ec \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7901  s\u7901  ng\u7885 c, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Hay l\'e0 t\'f4i th\'e1o xu\u7889 ng c\u7845 t l\u7841 i \u273 i, t\'f4i s\u7907  kh\'f4ng c\u7849 n th\u7853 n s\u7869  l\'e0m h\u7887 ng n\'f3, em s\u7869  \u273 au l\'f2ng, d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 v\u7853 t b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i cho em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quen thu\u7897 c th\'e1o ng\u7885 c b\u7897 i, c\u7845 t v\'e0o trong t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\u7915 a r\u7891 i ki\u7871 m c\u7899  n\'f3i \u273 \'f3i b\u7909 ng, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac ng\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t b\'e0n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i m\u7845 t kh\u7849 u v\u7883 , \u259 n v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng c\u361 ng th\u7845 y nh\u7841 t nh\u432  n\u432 \u7899 c \u7889 c, vui m\u7915 ng duy nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 qu\'e1 kh\u7913  h\u7871 t th\u7843 y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 gi\u7843 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7913 c \u259 n kh\'f4ng gi\u7843 . X\u432 \u417 ng s\u432 \u7901 n l\'e0 ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua c\u7853 u t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 i mua, t\u7915 ng th\u7899  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ch\'ednh c\u7853 u ch\u7885 n, h\'f4m nay x\'e0o v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng lo\u7841 i rau kh\'e1c, m\'f9i v\u7883  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879  l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'e0 l\'e0m kh\'f3 Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  m\u7895 i ng\'e0y ph\u7843 i l\'e0m c\u417 m cho c\u7853 u \u259 n. Theo \'fd ngh\u297  n\'e0y c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat chua x\'f3t n\u7893 i l\'ean, nh\u432 ng r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i kh\'f4ng g\u7841 t \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kia \u273 \'e8 xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u258 n c\u417 m xong Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng y\'ean r\u7917 a b\'e1t, lau kh\'f4, \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  trong b\u7871 p ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i; tr\u7903  ra ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch ng\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng \u273 \'f4\u777 i k\'eanh, nh\'ecn th\u7901 i gian t\u7915 ng ch\'fat tr\'f4i qua, trong l\'f2ng c\'e0ng tr\u7903  n\'ean lo l\u7855 ng b\u7845 t an, l\u7909 c ph\u7911  ng\u361  t\u7841 ng \u273 \u7873 u kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c co l\u7841 i th\'e0nh m\u7897 t \u273 o\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m nay l\uc0\u7841 i l\'e0 th\u7913  s\'e1u, d\u7921 a theo m\u7885 i khi, c\u7853 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7847 u hoan.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn ra manh m\u7889 i, l\'fac n\'e0y l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7847 m l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean mua cho h\u7855 n xem tin t\u7913 c, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean li\u7871 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7845 y c\u7853 u v\'f9i \u7903  m\u7897 t g\'f3c kh\'e1c tr\'ean s\'f4 pha, g\u7909 c \u273 \u7847 u, m\u7897 t ch\u7889 c l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\u7889 c li\'ean t\u7909 c \u273 \'f4\u777 i k\'eanh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7847 y c\'f5i l\'f2ng t\'e2m s\u7921 , t\u7911 i th\'e2n l\u7841 i \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u7891 i qua \u273 \'f3 \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c: "H\'f4m nay \u273 \u7871 n c\'f9ng l\'e0 l\'e0m sao? N\u7871 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n xem th\'ec ch\'fang ta \u273 i ng\u7911  \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\'edm m\'f4i d\uc0\u432 \u7899 i, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, t\'f9y \'fd Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m c\u7853 u d\u7853 y, \u7845 n t\u7855 t tivi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng tho\'e1ng c\'e1i kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ti\uc0\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi vu\u7889 t ve l\u432 ng c\u7853 u, gh\'e9 v\'e0o b\'ean tai c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "Kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng? C\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i c\u7913 ng th\'e0nh th\u7871  n\'e0y r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng th\u7843  l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng: "\u272 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m bao nhi\'eau l\u7847 n r\u7891 i, sao b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\u7841 i c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u432 ng ch\u7841 m v\'e0o ga gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7873 m m\u7841 i, m\'ed m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7899 p \u273 \u7897 ng, l\'fd tr\'ed \u273 \'e3 c\u259 ng th\'e0nh m\u7897 t s\u7907 i d\'e2y, nh\u432 ng th\'e2n th\u7875  r\u7891 i l\u7841 i theo th\'f3i quen l\'e0m ra \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i khe kh\u7869  \'97\'97 \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c quen thu\u7897 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, quen thu\u7897 c \'f4m \u226 \u769 p v\'e0 \u273 \u7909 ng ch\u7841 m, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\'f4 h\u7845 p, nh\u7883 p tim v\'e0 \u273 \u7897  \u7845 m ng\u7909 y trang n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 m\'e0 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\u7889 n ch\u7841 y, m\u7897 t b\'ean nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  \u273 ang \u273 \'e8 n\u7863 ng m\'ecnh c\u7847 u hoan m\'ecnh kia kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i; m\u7897 t b\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'e1ng c\u7921  m\'e0 th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n t\u7845 t c\u7843 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed t\u7915  trong \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c vui th\'edch v\'e0 kho\'e1i c\u7843 m b\u7843 n n\u259 ng \'97\'97 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi hi\u7875 u r\u7845 t r\'f5 c\u7853 u, m\u7885 i th\u7913  v\u7873  c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u n\u7857 m trong kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u li\u7873 u ch\u7871 t nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, quay \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" ph\'eda tr\'ean, ph\u7847 n c\u7893  cong l\'ean, kh\'f3e m\u7855 t nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7845 m ra n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t \'97\'97n\'f3i kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i l\'e0 v\'ec s\u7907  h\'e3i hay l\'e0 g\'ec c\'e1i g\'ec kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n ch\u7845 t l\u7887 ng tr\'ean kh\'f3e m\u7855 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 i th\u7903  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\uc0\u7889 ng ch\u7871  n\u7893 i r\'f9ng m\'ecnh m\u7897 t c\'e1i. V\'ec \u273 \u7875  che gi\u7845 u, cam ch\u7883 u m\'e0 ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng du\u7895 i hai tay \'f4m l\u7845 y "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" ph\'eda tr\'ean \u273 ang c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ch\u7863 t ch\u7869  t\u432 \u417 ng li\'ean...\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7917 a \u273 \'eam Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7903  m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t c\u7853 u b\'ecnh t\u297 nh m\'e0 thanh t\u7881 nh, kh\'f4ng ch\'fat n\'e0o bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 . C\u7853 u c\u7849 n th\u7853 n d\'e8 ch\u7915 ng l\'e9n nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7857 m \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang ng\u7911  say, d\'f9ng ch\u259 n \u273 em m\'ecnh lui l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f3 c\u7847 n ng\u7911  hay kh\'f4ng, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng b\'e0y ra b\u7897  d\u7841 ng t\u432  th\'e1i n\'e0y c\'f3 ph\u7843 i ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\'ec l\u7915 a g\u7841 t m\'ecnh hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u n\u7893 i t\'e2m t\u432  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, hao h\u7871 t t\'e2m t\u432  nh\u432  th\u7871  ng\u7909 y trang th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i di\u7877 n vai n\'e0y, c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7891  g\'ec \u273 \'e2y? N\u7871 u h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n l\u7845 y m\u7841 ng m\'ecnh, b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t m\u7845 y tr\u259 m l\u7847 n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng quan tr\u7885 ng. C\'f3 l\u7869  n\'f3 v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 b\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u7881  c\u7847 n ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i, c\u7913  b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng thanh s\u7855 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n h\u7915 ng \u273 \'f4ng ng\'e0y mai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7889 n cho l\'e0 m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c ng\u7911  m\u7845 t, khi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i th\'ec \u273 \'e3 ng\u7917 i th\u7845 y m\'f9i th\u417 m tr\u7913 ng r\'e1n v\'e0 c\'e0 ph\'ea.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i n\'f3i ti\u7871 p t\u7915  sau khi Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi hi\u7879 n h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i, trong nh\'e0 li\u7873 n c\'f3 th\'eam r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  m\'e1y pha c\'e0 ph\'ea, m\'e1y l\'e0m s\u7919 a \u273 \u7853 u n\'e0nh, m\'e1y \'e9p hoa qu\u7843 , m\'e1y l\'e0m s\u7919 a chua v\'e2n v\'e2n. Ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch ch\'ednh l\'e0 l\u7899 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  cho d\'f9 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927  c\u361 ng c\'f2n c\'f3 cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng th\'fa v\u7883  h\u417 n ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng l\'e0 m\'ecnh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , m\u7845 y th\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mua qua m\u7841 ng, v\u7853 y h\u7855 n l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o nh\u7853 n h\'e0ng, l\u7841 i c\'f2n ti\u7873 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2u ra?\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y th\'e2n \u7843 nh kia th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 c\u7913 ng l\u7841 i, s\u7907  h\'e3i nguy\'ean b\u7843 n h\u417 i h\u417 i bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a l\u417  l\u7917 ng d\'e2ng l\'ean, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\'ecn \u7903  trong m\u7855 t c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \'f4n nhu tu\u7845 n m\u7929  l\'fac n\'e0y l\u7841 i l\u7897  ra qu\u7927  kh\'ed d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u432 ng hai ph\u7847 n b\u7919 a s\'e1ng \u273 i t\u7899 i, theo th\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7879  h\u7841  m\u7897 t n\u7909  h\'f4n l\'ean tr\'e1n c\u7853 u: "Ch\'e0o bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng, mau \u273 i r\u7917 a m\u7863 t \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n c\'e1i h\'f4n ng\'e0y x\u432 a ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o, tay ch\'e2n c\u7913 ng nh\u7855 c \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng v\u7879  sinh, m\u7903  v\'f2i n\u432 \u7899 c, nghe ti\u7871 ng n\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7843 y r\'e0o r\'e0o, ch\u7889 ng hai tay l\'ean b\u7879  b\u7891 n r\u7917 a, m\u7899 i ph\'e1t gi\'e1c ra hai tay m\'ecnh \u273 ang kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c run r\u7849 y th\u7853 t nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 ph\u7847 n b\u7897 i ph\u7909 c ch\'ednh m\'ecnh h\'f4m qua. C\u361 ng may qua m\u7897 t l\'e1t n\u7919 a\'a0 t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'f3 th\u7875  k\u7871 t th\'fac r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i l\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\uc0\u7849 u v\u7883 , b\u7919 a s\'e1ng ch\u7881  \u259 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean ra v\u7867  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u7893 i l\u7841 i chi\u7871 c \'e1o s\u417  mi h\'f4m qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang thu d\u7885 n b\'e1t \u273 \u361 a, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\u7853 u \u259 n m\u7863 c ch\u7881 nh t\u7873  chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\'f3 ch\'fat kinh ng\u7841 c: "H\'f4m nay ph\u7843 i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u tr\'e1nh \'e1nh m\u7855 t h\u7855 n: "V\'e2ng, c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c em ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch x\u7843 y ra v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 o g\u7885 i em \u273 i l\'e0m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7887 i n\u7919 a: "V\u7853 y v\u7873  s\u7899 m ch\'fat. \u272 \'fang l\'fac trong nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7891  \u259 n l\u7855 m, em mu\u7889 n \u259 n g\'ec th\'ec nh\u7899  mua v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai th\uc0\u7845 p \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u259 m ph\'fat sau khi c\u7853 u \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t m\'ecnh d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\u7917 a s\u7893  ban c\'f4ng, nh\'ecn xe Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7841 y ra kh\u7887 i c\u7893 ng ti\u7875 u khu.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f4i c\uc0\u7911 a h\u7855 n v\u7851 n \'f4n nhu h\u417 i nh\u7871 ch l\'ean, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang c\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \'e1y m\u7855 t m\'e0u \u273 en l\u7841 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t m\u7843 nh t\u297 nh m\u7883 ch:\cb1 \
\cb3 "N\'f3i d\uc0\u7889 i. Th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng ngoan."\cb1 \
