\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi ng\uc0\u7891 i v\'e0o xe, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'ed l\u7841 nh t\u7915 ng ch\'fat m\u7897 t t\u7843 n ra ngo\'e0i, l\u7841 i t\u7915  t\u7915  b\u7883  n\'f3ng b\u7913 c th\'e1ng b\u7843 y xua tan.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai tay c\uc0\u7853 u che m\u7863 t, th\u7903  ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i th\u7853 t d\'e0i, sau m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u m\u7899 i h\'f2a ho\'e3n l\u7841 i, bu\'f4ng tay xu\u7889 ng, l\u7845 y ra t\u7915  trong t\'fai \'e1o m\u7897 t t\u7845 m danh thi\u7871 p c\u7921 c k\u7923  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m qua ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 qua loa nh\'e9t v\'e0o t\'fai, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn k\u7929 , l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ph\'eda tr\'ean ch\u7881  \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n in m\u7897 t c\'e1i t\'ean "\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n", b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t chu\u7895 i \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7881  vi\u7871 t tay, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  v\u7915 a m\u7899 i t\u7841 m th\u7901 i vi\u7871 t l\'ean, \u7903  ngay v\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i th\'e0nh ph\'eda \u273 \'f4ng T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e0u \u273 i\u7879 n ng\u7847 m, nh\u432 ng \u273 i hai chuy\u7871 n xe bus l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7871 n, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 ch\'fat \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7845 t l\u7841 i danh thi\u7871 p v\'e0o trong t\'fai, nh\u7853 p \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7881  v\'e0o \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7841 y theo tuy\u7871 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7881  d\u7851 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4 D\'e2n th\uc0\u7883  m\u7845 y n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u361 ng m\u7841 nh m\u7869  th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n ki\u7871 n thi\u7871 t \u273 \'f4 th\u7883 , n\u7897 i th\'e0nh m\u7903  r\u7897 ng h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u, m\u7863 c d\'f9 v\u7851 n k\'e9m kh\'f4ng \'edt so v\u7899 i Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  l\'e2n c\u7853 n, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng l\'e0 x\u432 a kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng nay. Khi c\'f2n nh\u7887  Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i s\u7889 ng \u7903  khu n\u7897 i th\'e0nh c\u361  b\'ean n\'e0y, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i khu m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng quen thu\u7897 c l\u7855 m, l\'e1i xe \u273 i n\u7917 a gi\u7901  m\u7899 i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7881  tr\'ean danh thi\u7871 p\'97\'97 l\'e0 m\u7897 t khu bi\u7879 t th\u7921  m\u7899 i x\'e2y g\u7847 n hai n\u259 m.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Sau khi ghi danh \uc0\u7903  c\u7893 ng ra v\'e0o, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i l\'e1i xe v\'f2ng trong ti\u7875 u khu m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat m\u7899 i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f2a nh\'e0 vi\u7871 t tr\'ean danh thi\u7871 p kia, c\u7853 u c\'f3 ch\'fat lo l\u7855 ng b\u7845 t an ti\u7871 n l\'ean nh\u7845 n chu\'f4ng c\u7917 a, m\u7903  c\u7917 a c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i v\u7883  l\'e3o nh\'e2n ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i, m\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  h\u417 n b\u7889 n m\u432 \u417 i tu\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7845 y danh thi\u7871 p ra, cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\'ecn: "Con t\'ecm l\'e3o ti\'ean sinh \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n \u7841 , ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua \'f4ng \u7845 y cho con t\u7845 m danh thi\u7871 p n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o c\u7917 a, h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean trong n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng ti\'ean sinh, l\'e0 kh\'e1ch nh\'e2n c\u7911 a ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o c\uc0\u7917 a qu\u7843  nhi\'ean tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y v\u7883  l\'e3o nh\'e2n ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua \u273 ang ng\u7891 i tr\'ean s\'f4 pha, v\u7851 n m\u7863 c ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \'f3, \u273 ang \u273 eo k\'ednh l\'e3o xem b\'e1o. Sau khi th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i v\'e0o \'f4ng li\u7873 n bu\'f4ng b\'e1o v\'e0 k\'ednh m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng, \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "Ta \u273 o\'e1n l\'e0 c\u7853 u s\u7869  \u273 \u7871 n m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  l\'fac n\'e3y \u273 \'e3 pha tr\'e0 xong b\u432 ng l\'ean, \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia quay \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i b\'e0: "Ch\u7883  Qu\u7871 , h\'f4m nay kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec n\u7919 a, ch\u7883  v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i. Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t ng\'e0y mai ch\u7883  c\u361 ng ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i \u273 i, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7883  Qu\u7871  \u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn s\uc0\u7855 p x\u7871 p b\'e0i tr\'ed b\u7889 n ph\'eda xung quanh m\u7897 t l\u432 \u7907 t: "Ng\'e0i \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y?" C\u7853 u r\u7845 t kinh ng\u7841 c T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883  c\'f2n c\u7845 t gi\u7845 u m\u7897 t v\u7883  cao nh\'e2n nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\'e0 b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 i ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n xua xua tay: "L\u7847 n n\'e0y ta t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng l\'e0 b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta nh\u7901  v\u7843  x\u7917  l\'fd m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c, nh\'e0 c\u7911 a b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u, quanh n\u259 m kh\'f4ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, v\u7915 a v\u7863 n cho ta m\u432 \u7907 n \u7903  hai ng\'e0y, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'fang l\'fac g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua b\u7897  d\'e1ng l\'e3o nh\'e2n g\u7845 p g\'e1p v\u7899 i c\'e2u "C\u7913 u ng\u432 \u7901 i", h\u7887 i: "Chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a ng\'e0i \u273 \'e3 xong r\u7891 i \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "V\u7851 n ph\u7843 i \u273 a t\u7841  ti\u7875 u huynh \u273 \u7879  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'e3 gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , h\u7919 u kinh v\'f4 hi\u7875 m."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (h\uc0\u7919 u kinh v\'f4 hi\u7875 m: chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'e1ng lo nh\u432 ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nguy hi\u7875 m g\'ec)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7843 i quy\u7871 t xong l\'e0 t\u7889 t r\u7891 i, d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n li\'ean quan t\u7899 i m\'ecnh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ti\u7879 n h\u7887 i nhi\u7873 u. C\u7853 u \u273 \u7847 y l\'f2ng t\'e2m s\u7921 , nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, n\'e2ng ch\'e9n tr\'e0 l\'ean y\'ean l\u7863 ng u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t h\u7899 p, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7893  h\u7885 ng kh\'f4 n\'f3ng \'97\'97m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i l\'f2ng nh\u432  l\u7917 a \u273 \u7889 t l\'e1i xe \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y, \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  ra chuy\u7879 n u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng h\u7887 i n\'f3i: "Ta \u273 o\'e1n kh\'f4ng sai, h\'f4m qua ti\u7875 u huynh \u273 \u7879  c\'f3 ph\'f9 Thanh T\'e2m c\u7911 a ta, c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn th\u7845 u th\u7913  kia r\u7891 i, n\'ean m\u7899 i t\u7899 i t\'ecm ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua th\u7847 n tr\'ed \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c r\'f5 r\'e0ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 b\u7903 i l\'e3o ti\'ean sinh n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i ng\u7897  ra h\'f3a ra \'f4ng \u273 \'e3 th\u7915 a d\u7883 p m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd m\'e0 nh\'e9t ph\'f9 Thanh T\'e2m cho m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia v\u432 \u417 n tay \u273 i\u7875 m m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\'ean b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u: "B\'ecnh n\'e0y \u273 \'fang l\'e0 \u273 \u7921 ng tro c\u7889 t c\u7911 a th\u7913  kia?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, l\'e0m theo l\u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ph\'e2n ph\'f3 th\'e1o b\'ecnh s\u7913  xu\u7889 ng. Ch\u7881  th\u7845 y \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n l\u7841 i l\u7845 y ra hai l\'e1 b\'f9a, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u m\u7897 t trong m\u7897 t ngo\'e0i cu\u7889 n l\u7841 i b\'ecnh s\u7913  kia, \u273 \u7875  \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'e2n l\'fac n\'e0y k\uc0\u7875  t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n \u273 u\'f4i chuy\u7879 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n t\u7915  nh\u7887  th\'e2n th\u7875  h\u432  nh\u432 \u7907 c, Tr\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  m\'ecnh mang tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng b\'e0i v\u7883  trong nh\'e0. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7889 c, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  \'e1m l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 v\u7883  l\'e3o nh\'e2n n\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn ra manh m\u7889 i, d\u7921 a v\'e0o kinh nghi\u7879 m nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra v\u7883  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o ti\'ean sinh n\'e0y l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh, b\'e2y gi\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7913 u m\'ecnh e r\u7857 ng c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 \'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n nghe xong v\'f4 c\'f9ng \u273 au x\'f3t \u273 \u7853 p m\u7841 nh l\'ean \u273 \'f9i: "H\u7891  \u273 \u7891 ! Sao c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7881  cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p nh\u432  v\u7853 y! H\u7855 n v\u7853 y l\'e0 ch\u7881  m\u7899 i h\u7885 c s\u417  s\'e0i, bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t m\'e0 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t hai! Ngh\u297  c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  khi c\'f2n s\u7889 ng \u273 \'e3 mang h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7899 ng \'e1c qu\u7927 , sau khi ch\u7871 t mang tro c\u7889 t b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7841 i cung ph\u7909 ng b\'e0i v\u7883  ng\'e0y \u273 \'eam, l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng d\u7851 n t\u7899 i \'e1c qu\u7843 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c L\u432 u \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng tr\'ean n\'fai T\'e2y Thanh kia c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i l\u7901 i t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng tin, chuy\u7879 n t\u7899 i b\'e2y gi\u7901  h\u7889 i h\u7853 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 mu\u7897 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n h\u7887 i c\u7853 u: "B\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o? D\u7921  \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Mu\uc0\u7889 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, "\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 mu\u7889 n ti\u7877 n v\u7883  n\'e0y \u273 i, ch\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ng\'e0i c\'f3 bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p n\'e0o,"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, bi\u7875 u th\u7883  \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7847 n ch\u7915  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, l\u7841 i b\u7893  sung: "C\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c... Ban \u273 \u7847 u l\'e0 con v\'ec m\'ecnh m\'e0 qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y y\'ean \u7893 n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p ti\'ean sinh, n\'f3i cho c\'f9ng l\'e0 con sai tr\u432 \u7899 c. Xin ng\'e0i \u273 \u7915 ng l\'e0m t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng h\u7855 n, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n ti\u7877 n h\u7855 n \u273 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng c\u7853 u b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u t\u7915  nh\u7887 , nh\u432 ng k\u7923  th\u7853 t \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i qu\u7927  th\u7847 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 i s\'e2u nghi\'ean c\u7913 u, cho d\'f9 c\'e1ch nh\'ecn nh\u7853 n x\u7917  l\'fd c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng h\'f2a th\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7841 o s\u297  t\u7915  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 n c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nhau. C\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432  v\u7853 y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c coi l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec, ng\u432 \u7901 i sau khi ch\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\'f3 linh h\u7891 n t\u7891 n t\u7841 i hay kh\'f4ng, c\'f3 lu\'e2n h\u7891 i chuy\u7875 n th\u7871  hay kh\'f4ng. N\u7871 u c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\'ean TV chi\u7871 u, si\'eau \u273 \u7897  cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\'e3ng sanh, \u273 \u7875  h\u7855 n quay v\u7873  n\u417 i n\'ean \u273 i, quay v\u7873  qu\u7929  t\'edch nguy\'ean b\u7843 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n th\'ec t\u7889 t r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i l\u7845 y ra m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9 v\'e0 m\u7897 t h\u7897 p di\'eam \u273 \u432 a cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u7853 u \u273 \u7889 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9 n\'e0y h\'f2a v\'e0o n\u432 \u7899 c, l\u7841 i ngh\u297  bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p d\u7909  th\u7913  kia u\u7889 ng l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7901 i ngu mu\u7897 i l\u7841 i ng\'f4ng cu\u7891 ng, lu\'f4n t\u432 \u417 \u777 ng t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7853 t, l\'f2ng d\u7841  l\u7841 i t\u7921  cho l\'e0 thi\u7879 n l\u432 \u417 ng. \'c1c qu\u7927  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, th\u7853 m ch\'ed ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng m\'ea ho\u7863 c ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  si\'eau \u273 \u7897 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  di\u7879 t tr\u7915  ch\'fang m\u7899 i l\'e0 bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p duy nh\u7845 t. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i n\'f3i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, l\'e0m c\u7853 u ta t\u259 ng th\'eam phi\u7873 n n\'e3o, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'f3 khi h\u7887 ng vi\u7879 c, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i n\u432 \u417 ng tay h\u7841 i ch\'ednh m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7843  kinh: "\'dd ng\'e0i l\'e0... \u273 \u7875  con m\u7897 t m\'ecnh tr\u7903  l\u7841 i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "N\u7871 u c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7885 c \u273 \u7841 o r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  ta, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i s\u7869  khi\u7871 n th\u7913  kia c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c. \u272 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 n\u7871 u mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7897  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 \u7897 ng tay \u273 \u7897 ng ch\'e2n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng." \'d4ng s\u7889 ng h\u417 n n\u7917 a \u273 \u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, am hi\u7875 u th\'e2m s\'e2u c\'e1ch c\'e2u th\'f4ng, l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7889  \'fd d\'f9ng l\u7901 i g\'e2y hi\u7875 u sai, khi\u7871 n cho ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t cho r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh khi\u7871 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c ph\'f9 l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng m\'e0 \u273 \u7897  th\u7913  kia, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng s\u7869  ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7917  d\u7909 ng v\u361  l\u7921 c di\u7879 t tr\u7915  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. Nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  bi\u7871 t r\u7857 ng b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n k\u7871 t qu\u7843  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng v\u7851 n gi\u7889 ng nhau, th\u7913  kia \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n t\u7891 n t\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean sinh ra dao \u273 \u7897 ng, n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i ph\u7843 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  l\u7847 n n\u7919 a m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng gi\u7843 m \u273 i m\u7845 y ph\u7847 n, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m kh\u7869  c\u7855 n r\u259 ng \u273 ang mu\u7889 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 a cho c\u7853 u hai t\u7845 m ph\'f9: "N\u7871 u s\u7921  t\'ecnh c\'f3 bi\u7871 n, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7921 a v\'e0o hai t\u7845 m ph\'f9 n\'e0y ch\u7841 y tho\'e1t ra ngo\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n t\u7915  d\'f2ng kh\'ed \u273 en kia \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn ra th\u7913  ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i n\'e0y r\u432 \u7899 c ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng d\u7877  \u273 \u7889 i ph\'f3, n\u7871 u c\'f3 th\u7875  \'f4ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n sinh th\'eam r\u7855 c r\u7889 i. M\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c ph\'f9 c\u7911 a t\u7845 m "Ph\'f9 tr\u7845 n t\'e0" kia b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n l\'e0 \'e1c qu\u7927  g\'ec, th\'e2n qu\u7927  tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u259 n v\'e0o ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng l\uc0\u7841 i l\u7845 y s\u7907 i d\'e2y chuy\u7873 n treo b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  qu\u7845 n trong b\'f9a kia ra \u273 \u432 a cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 \u7875  tr\'e1nh cho th\u7913  kia sinh nghi, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u c\u7913  \u273 eo l\'ean \u273 \'e3, ch\u7901  s\u7921  t\'ecnh gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t xong th\'ec tr\u7843  l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897  h\u7855 n l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean si\uc0\u7871 t ch\u7863 t ba t\u7845 m ph\'f9 v\'e0 h\u7897 p di\'eam, chia ra c\u7845 t v\'e0o trong t\'fai qu\u7847 n, l\u7841 i mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i t\u7841  \u417 n v\u7899 i \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia r\u7891 i m\u7899 i c\'e1o t\u7915  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
