\cb3 Sau khi \uc0\u273 i ra t\u7915  ch\u7895  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o ti\'ean sinh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng v\u7873  th\u7859 ng nh\'e0 m\'e0 l\'e1i xe v\'f4 \u273 \u7883 nh trong n\u7897 i th\'e0nh h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac c\'f2n nh\uc0\u7887  \u7903  nh\'e0 v\u7899 i b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i c\'f9ng xem kinh k\u7883 ch B\u7841 ch X\'e0 truy\u7879 n, kh\'f4ng th\'edch nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 H\u7913 a Ti\'ean, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng g\'e1nh v\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'ecnh c\u7843 m \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i \'e1i nh\'e2n, c\u361 ng ch\u7883 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7917  th\'e1ch, th\'ea t\u7917  trong nh\'e0 c\'f2n \u273 ang mang thai, sau khi h\u7855 n ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\'ea t\u7917  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p b\u7883  d\u7885 a ch\u7871 t, \u273 \u7871 n khi \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7913 u s\u7889 ng r\u7891 i th\u7853 m ch\'ed ngay c\u7843  nh\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng v\u7873 , tr\u7889 n th\u7859 ng v\'e0o trong mi\u7871 u. N\u7871 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i v\'ec h\u7855 n tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh, th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  kh\'f4ng tin t\u432 \u7903 ng \'e1i nh\'e2n, v\u7873  sau l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  th\u7871 ? B\u7841 ch N\u432 \u417 ng T\u7917  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i ch\u7883 u \u273 au kh\u7893  nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\'f2n ph\u7843 i tr\'f4ng c\u7853 y nhi t\u7917  t\u7899 i c\u7913 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n khi chuy\u7879 n x\u7843 y ra v\u7899 i ch\'ednh m\'ecnh, b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\u7899 i c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ai c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n s\u7921  th\u7853 t b\u7841 n \u273 \u7901 i \u7903  nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hu\uc0\u7889 ng chi Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i B\u7841 ch N\u432 \u417 ng T\u7917 . B\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 duy\'ean ti\u7873 n \u273 \u7883 nh g\u7863 p g\u7905  tr\'ean c\u7847 u \u272 o\u7841 n Ki\u7873 u l\'e3ng m\u7841 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, nh\u7919 ng g\'ec c\'f3 ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\'ecnh t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\u7845 y tro c\u7889 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ta v\u7873  mang tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\'e0 "H\u7855 n" b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng thanh s\u7855 c ti\u7873 m ph\u7909 c b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, d\u7877  d\'e0ng m\'ea t\'e2m m\'ecnh\'97\'97 l\'fac n\'e0y ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n to\'e0n th\'e2n v\u7851 n ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u7891 n nh\u432  bay ra ngo\'e0i, c\'f3 ch\'fat th\u7845 t th\u7847 n m\'e0 ngh\u297 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng mang con c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\'ecnh c\u361 ng c\'f3 kha\u777  n\u259 ng mang con c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ngh\u297  kh\'f4ng ra t\u7841 i sao m\'ecnh v\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\u7841 i ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n ra quan h\u7879  ki\u7873 u di\u7877 m nh\u432  th\u7871 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng d\'e1m x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh, n\'e0y c\'f3 ph\u7843 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t v\'f2ng \u273 \'f9a b\u7905 n tr\u7843  th\'f9 c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng n\'ean d\'f9ng t\'e2m ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 o\'e1n ma qu\u7927 , kh\'f4ng n\'ean y\'eau c\u7847 u xa v\u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  con ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m t\'ecnh y\'eau. \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 l\u7901 i m\u7897 t v\u7883  \u273 \u7841 o tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c khuy\'ean b\u7843 o c\u7853 u, c\u361 ng l\'e0 nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c chung c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng "Cao nh\'e2n" xua qu\u7927  tr\u7915  ma c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u361  m\'ed m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng, s\u7901  l\'ean t\u7845 m ph\'f9 tr\u7845 n t\'e0 trong t\'fai \'e1o. D\'f9 sao, h\'f4m nay t\u7845 t c\u7843  s\u7869  k\u7871 t th\'fac. T\u7915  nay v\u7873  sau, b\u7885 n h\u7885  ki\u7873 u quy ki\u7873 u, l\u7897  quy l\u7897 , nhi\u7873 u nh\u7845 t c\'f9ng l\u7855 m l\'e0 ng\'e0y l\u7877  ng\'e0y t\u7871 t s\u7869  l\u7863 ng l\u7869  \u273 i th\u259 m m\u7897  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\'e9t t\u432 \u7899 c t\u7871  b\'e1i cho h\u7855 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n\'97\'97 tuy r\u7857 ng th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7853 u ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng quang minh ch\'ednh \u273 \u7841 i \u273 i t\u7871  b\'e1i th\'e2n ph\u7853 n h\u7855 n.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (ki\uc0\u7873 u quy ki\u7873 u, l\u7897  quy l\u7897 : \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i l\'e0 ai \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3, kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n nhau)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i tr\u432 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f2ng quanh b\'ean ngo\'e0i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7849 u v\u7883  \u259 n c\u417 m, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac g\u7847 n \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  tan l\'e0m nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi m\u7899 i l\'e1i xe \u273 \u7871 n si\'eau th\u7883  hay \u273 i mua t\'f4m v\'e0 rau qu\u7843  t\u432 \u417 i h\'f4m \u273 \'f3, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi mang theo m\u7897 t t\'fai \u273 \u7847 y nguy\'ean li\u7879 u n\u7845 u \u259 n v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 \'fang gi\u7901  c\u417 m \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a nh\'e0 m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7903  c\u7917 a, nh\u7853 n t\'fai nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua, tr\'e1ch c\u7913  n\'f3i: "Sao l\u7841 i mua t\'f4m? Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i n\'f3i sau n\'e0y s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m thu\u7927  h\u7843 i s\u7843 n cho em n\u7919 a sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c bu\u7897 t mi\u7879 ng: "Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 h\'f4m nay r\u7845 t t\u432 \u417 i! ... Ch\u7881  \u259 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao... m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ngh\u297 , v\u7873  sau m\u7863 c k\u7879  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i hay qu\u7927 , s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai quan t\'e2m nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u n\u7919 a, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai n\u7845 u c\u417 m cho c\u7853 u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7871 t c\'e1ch nh\'ecn c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i, l\u7845 y m\u7897 t chai r\u432 \u7907 u vang t\u7915  trong t\'fai ra \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean b\'e0n: "Sao l\u7841 i c\'f2n mua r\u432 \u7907 u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean mi\uc0\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "H\'f4m nay cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, mang \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 i v\'e0o trong b\u7871 p, sau \u273 \'f3 trong b\u7871 p vang l\'ean ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u777 a tu\u777  la\u803 nh \u273 \'f3ng m\u7903 , ti\u7871 p theo l\'e0 ti\u7871 ng th\'e1i th\u7883 t, ti\u7871 ng b\'e1t ch\u7853 u va ch\u7841 m, ti\u7871 ng m\'e1y h\'fat kh\'f3i c\'f9ng v\u7899 i ti\u7871 ng x\'e8o x\'e8o l\'fac th\u7913 c \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c cho v\'e0o n\u7891 i. \'c2m thanh m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, b\'e2y gi\u7901  nghe th\u7845 y r\u7891 i l\u7841 i sinh ra c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7891 ng d\u7841 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng ng\u7889 c trong ch\u7889 c l\'e1t m\u7899 i kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c \'fd th\u7913 c l\u7847 n n\u7919 a. C\u7853 u l\u7845 y hai chi\u7871 c ly t\u7915  tr\'ean t\u7911  r\u432 \u7907 u \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean b\'e0n c\u417 m, l\u7845 y ra t\u7915  trong t\'fai \'e1o t\u7845 m ph\'f9 tr\u7845 n t\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7853 p th\'e0nh h\'ecnh tam gi\'e1c, b\u7887  v\'e0o ly tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, d\'f9ng di\'eam \u273 \u7889 t, nh\'ecn tro t\'e0n m\'e0u x\'e1m nh\u7841 t r\u417 i \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \'e1y ly, l\u7841 i r\'f3t \u273 \u7847 y r\u432 \u7907 u vang cho hai ly r\u432 \u7907 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tro c\uc0\u7911 a t\u7845 m ph\'f9 kia qu\u7843  nhi\'ean kh\'e1c v\u7899 i tro c\u7911 a gi\u7845 y th\u432 \u7901 ng, sau khi \u273 \u7893  ch\u7845 t l\u7887 ng v\'e0o, tho\'e1ng lay \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat li\u7873 n tan h\u7871 t v\'e0o trong r\u432 \u7907 u, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  th\u7845 y n\u7917 a \u273 i\u7875 m d\u7845 u v\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi l\'e0m xong t\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  c\u7853 u m\u7899 i \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u7903  nh\'e0, \u273 i ra gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7885 i ng\'e0y x\u7899 i c\u417 m s\u7861 n ch\u7901  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y n\u7871 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n ch\u432 a l\'e0m xong \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  \u273 i v\'e0o b\u7871 p, nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi x\'e0o rau, gi\'fap b\u432 ng canh b\u432 ng th\u7913 c ra ngo\'e0i. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng ch\'ea c\u7853 u v\u432 \u7899 ng v\'edu, l\u7841 i s\u7907  kh\'f3i d\u7847 u l\'e0m c\u7853 u ngh\u7865 n, nh\u432 ng l\'e0 xua c\u361 ng xua kh\'f4ng \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m nay \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c s\'e1ng su\u7889 t bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c ch\u7881  h\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\u7889 n th\u7853 t xa, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 n l\'ean ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i hai l\u432 \u7907 t b\u432 ng ba m\'f3n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n m\'f4\u803 t ch\'e9n canh ra: "Th\u7845 y em vui v\u7867 , h\'f4m nay \u273 \u7891  \u259 n mua v\u7873  c\u361 ng nhi\u7873 u, t\u7841 m th\u7901 i t\u259 ng th\'eam m\u7897 t m\'f3n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'e2ng ly \uc0\u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i tay h\u7855 n: "V\'e2ng, c\u7841 n ly." N\'f3i xong xong c\u7847 m l\u7845 y ly c\u7911 a m\'ecnh nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng c\u7909 ng c\u7909 ng ly th\u7911 y tinh trong tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\'e2ng l\'ean u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i ch\u7881  \u432 u nh\'e3 m\'e0 th\u7853 n tr\u7885 ng nh\u7845 p m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m nh\u7887 , bu\'f4ng ly h\u417 i cong m\u7855 t l\'ean nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i, sao l\u7841 i g\u7845 p g\'e1p \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i u\u7889 ng r\u432 \u7907 u th\u7871  n\'e0y. Say r\u7891 i mu\u7889 n t\'f4i l\'e0m g\'ec sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhanh ch\'f3ng l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u l\u7855 c l\u7855 c: "C\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n l\'e0m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'edp m\u7855 t li\u7871 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn ch\u7845 t l\u7887 ng trong ly th\u7911 y tinh gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  h\u7891 ng b\u7843 o th\u7841 ch ch\u7853 m r\'e3i xoay th\'e0nh xo\'e1y, n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i: "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng u\u7889 ng, tr\u7915  khi em \u273 \'fat t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'e1i g\'ec?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean, m\u7903  to m\u7855 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i ng\u7843  v\u7873  sau, l\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 ng t\u7921 a l\u432 ng v\'e0o gh\u7871 , v\u7895  v\u7895  ch\'e2n m\'ecnh, hai m\u7855 t t\u7889 i tr\u7847 m nh\'ecn ch\u259 m ch\'fa Tr\'ec Di\'ean, kh\u7869  m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i: "B\u7843 o b\u7889 i, t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y ng\u7891 i, \u273 \'fat t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nu\uc0\u7889 t m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y m\uc0\u7885 i \'fd ngh\u297  trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u l\'e0 mu\u7889 n khi\u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi u\u7889 ng ly r\u432 \u7907 u kia, ch\u7881  ch\u7847 n ch\u7915  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, ngoan ngo\'e3n ng\u7891 i t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7853 p t\u7913 c v\u432 \u417 n tay k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, m\u361 i d\'e1n l\'ean ph\u7847 n c\u7893  l\u7897  ra c\u7911 a c\u7853 u th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng c\u432 \u7901 i, m\u7863 t m\'e0y nhu h\'f2a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u417 i th\u7903  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, r\u7909 t c\u7893  m\u7897 t c\'e1i, r\u361  m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u432 a tay v\u7899 i ly r\u432 \u7907 u tr\'ean b\'e0n. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m c\u7853 u r\u7845 t ch\u7863 t, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng l\u7921 c c\u7921 a qu\u7853 y nghi\'eang v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7875  v\u7899 i \'97\'97 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean d\'f9ng s\u7913 c c\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i l\'ean c\'e1i c\u7893  nho nh\u7887  c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\u7847 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\'e9n r\u432 \u7907 u, quay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i n\'e2ng r\u432 \u7907 u mu\u7889 n \u273 \'fat Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i nghi\'eang \u273 i, m\u7855 t ch\u7913 a \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean, d\'f9ng mi\u7879 ng \u273 \'fat." Thanh \'e2m th\u7845 p \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n x\u432 \u417 ng, t\u7915 ng tia t\u7915 ng tia m\'ea ho\u7863 c nh\'e2n t\'e2m, tho\'e1ng nh\u432  Hoa y\'eau d\u432 \u7899 i ho\'e0ng tuy\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 \uc0\u273 ang trong t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i tho\u7855 t c\'e1i \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u ng\u7853 m m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m r\u432 \u7907 u, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, d\u7921 a theo c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  t\u7915  l\u7841 i g\u7847 n h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn dung m\u7841 o c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n kia, c\u432 \u7901 i th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, \u273 \u432 a tay \u7845 n l\'ean g\'e1y Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng h\'f4n l\'ean m\'f4i c\u7853 u. R\u432 \u7907 u \u7903  gi\u7919 a r\u259 ng m\'f4i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7843 y xu\'f4i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi thu\u7853 n theo h\'e9 mi\u7879 ng, m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng to\'e0n b\u7897  r\u432 \u7907 u \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'fat qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i v\u7851 n nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, m\u7897 t tay c\u7847 m ly r\u432 \u7907 u, tay kia kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o \u273 \'e3 v\'f2ng l\'ean c\u7893  v\'e0 l\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  ch\'ednh m\'ecnh. M\u7897 t ly r\u432 \u7907 u nh\u7887  d\u7847 n d\u7847 n th\u7845 y \u273 \'e1y, hai m\u7855 t c\u7853 u nh\u7855 m ch\u7863 t, kh\'f3e m\u7855 t r\u7891 i l\u7841 i tr\'e0n ra gi\u7885 t n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t trong su\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4n \u273 i n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t tr\'ean kh\'f3e m\u7855 t c\u7853 u: "\u272 ang t\u7889 t th\u7871  n\'e0o l\u7841 i kh\'f3c r\u7891 i, nghe l\u7901 i, m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra. M\u7863 t em \u273 \u7887  nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'e0m g\'ec, \u273 \u7915 ng v\u7897 i, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i s\u7869  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 \'f2i n\u7907 , tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u259 n c\u417 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng giam c\u7847 m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, ch\u7881  v\u7851 n d\'f9ng m\u7897 t tay kh\u7869  \'f4m c\u7853 u tr\'e1nh cho c\u7853 u t\'e9 xu\u7889 ng, th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, m\u7899 i kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean a, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 t\'f4i n\'f3i, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i em mu\u7889 n \u7903  trong ng\u7921 c t\'f4i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac n\'e0y m\uc0\u7899 i cu\u7889 ng qu\'edt \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ch\u7895  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, trong l\'fac v\u7897 i v\'e0ng th\u7853 m ch\'ed thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a v\u7845 p v\'e0o chi\u7871 c gh\u7871  b\'ean c\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7843 n nhi\'ean thong th\u7843  c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u259 n c\u417 m xong, th\u7853 m ch\'ed t\u7921 a h\u7891  r\u7845 t c\'f3 d\'e3 v\u7885 ng \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i l\u7841 i \u273 \'fat cho h\u7855 n hai ly r\u432 \u7907 u, r\'f5 r\'e0ng r\u7845 t vui v\u7867  chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7891 i l\u7841 i nu\u7889 t kh\'f4ng tr\'f4i, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \'e2m th\u7847 m quan s\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i gian t\u7915 ng ch\'fat t\u7915 ng ch\'fat tr\'f4i qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\'ecnh y\'ean v\'f4 s\u7921  thu d\u7885 n b\'e0n \u259 n, c\u7885  n\u7891 i r\u7917 a b\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u xem \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 hai gi\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 t\u7915  ph\u7853 p ph\'f2ng lo l\u7855 ng s\u7907  h\'e3i s\u7907  b\u7845 t an bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh \u273 \u7847 y l\'f2ng nghi ng\u7901  \'97\'97\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia kia c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\'f3 th\u7875  nhanh ch\'f3ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 u c\'f2n ph\'e1 gi\u7843 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thu\u7853 t m\'ea th\u7847 n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 b\'e1n ph\'f9 gi\u7843  ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i \'f4ng n\'f3i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c ph\'f9 kia l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c si\'eau \u273 \u7897  \u432 , v\'ec sao \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  v\u7851 n ch\u432 a c\'f3 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, n\u7871 u l\'e0 thu\u7889 c c\u7843 m th\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  r\u7891 i m\'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tin ch\uc0\u7855 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7889 t nh\u7847 m ph\'f9, ngh\u297  \u273 i ngh\u297  l\u7841 i, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  l\'e0 v\'ec m\'ecnh \u273 \'fat Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi u\u7889 ng ly r\u432 \u7907 u kia, \u273 i qua d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed, v\'ec v\u7853 y d\u7851 n \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f9 m\u7845 t hi\u7879 u l\u7921 c?\cb1 \
\cb3 Lo\uc0\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o n\'f3i v\u7899 i \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o ti\'ean sinh \u273 \'e2y?\cb1 \
