\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao, t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  v\u7851 n xem k\'eanh trung \u432 \u417 ng ngh\u297  chuy\u7879 n, xem \u273 \'e3 ba gi\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u h\u7887 i c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean, em b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'edch xem k\'eanh trung \u432 \u417 ng t\u7915  khi n\'e0o v\u7853 y? V\u7851 n ch\u7881  xem m\u7897 t k\'eanh?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng h\u7855 n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean vang l\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c t\u7855 t ph\u7909 t ti vi, m\u7903  to m\u7855 t quay l\u7841 i nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  con th\u7887  b\u7883  gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n t\u7915  trong tay c\u7853 u: "T\u7855 t th\'ec t\u7855 t, c\u361 ng n\'ean \u273 i ng\u7911  r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u361 ng kh\'ed \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  "Em ng\u7911  s\'f4 pha". C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng m\u7885 i ng\'e0y l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7903 i qu\u7847 n \'e1o k\'e9o ch\u259 n chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ng\u7911  m\'e0 l\u7899 n gan \u273 \u7849 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang mu\u7889 n k\'e9o c\u7853 u qua, n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t ch\u259 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, h\'f4m qua \u273 \'e3 m\u7879 t qu\'e1 r\u7891 i, h\'f4m nay mu\u7889 n ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m nay c\uc0\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  s\u7907  b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng gi\u7843  v\u7901  n\u7893 i m\'e0 tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p s\u7909 p \u273 \u7893  ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 n... Sau \u273 \'f3, b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra t\u7845 t c\u7843  b\u7855 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 ch\u7901  \u273 \'f3n b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7869  l\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec, l\u7841 i b\u7903 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t g\'ec, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \'e2m th\u7847 m t\u7921  m\'ecnh suy \u273 o\'e1n m\'e0 c\'e0ng th\'eam s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean t\u7853 n l\u7921 c duy tr\'ec b\u7873  ngo\'e0i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y, \'edt nh\u7845 t c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'e0 an to\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi cu\u7889 n ch\u259 n \u273 em c\u7853 u cu\u7897 n th\'e0nh m\u7897 t c\u7909 c, kh\'f4ng vui c\'e1ch ch\u259 n ch\u7885 t b\u7909 ng c\u7853 u: "\u272 \'e3 n\'f3i bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i tr\u7843  n\u7907 , l\u7841 i qu\u7925 t n\u7907 ." Nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng c\u7913  v\u7853 y m\'e0 k\'e9o m\u7897 t g\'f3c ch\u259 n ra, t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n n\u7857 m b\'ean c\u7853 u ng\u7911 , ch\u7881  v\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361  \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u bu\'f4ng, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng l\u7841 i h\'f4n h\'f4n m\u7863 t v\u7899 i v\'e0nh tai c\u7853 u, qua h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i ng\u7915 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7919  im l\u7863 ng nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i m\u7863 c h\u7855 n l\'e0m, b\'ean tai v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac h\'f4n c\u7853 u tr\'eau ch\u7885 c c\u7853 u v\'e0 ti\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\u7889 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n. C\u7853 u r\u361  l\'f4ng mi, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  c\'f3 qu\u7927  nh\'e0 ai \u273 \'f2i n\u7907  d\'f9ng ph\u432 \u417 ng ph\'e1p \u273 \'f2i n\u7907  th\u7871  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\u7903  ph\'e0o nh\u7865  nh\'f5m.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u nh\u432  h\u7871 t th\u7843 y nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 gi\u7843  v\u7901 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 b\u7841 n \u273 \u7901 i t\u7889 t ng\'e0n d\u7863 m m\u7899 i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t, c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f3 c\u7847 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Nh\u432 ng t\u7915  nh\u7887  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t, l\u7901 i n\'f3i v\'e0 vi\u7879 c l\'e0m c\u7911 a qu\u7927 , m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean tin. Ch\'fang ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t d\u7885 a ng\u432 \u417 i, b\u7913 c hi\u7871 p ng\u432 \u417 i, d\u7909  d\u7895  ng\u432 \u417 i, l\u7915 a g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u417 i... Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng d\u7851 n ng\u432 \u417 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xuy\'ean qua khe h\uc0\u7903  r\'e8m c\u7917 a s\u7893  d\u7877  d\'e0ng tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t v\u7847 ng tr\u259 ng tr\'f2n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean y\'ean l\u7863 ng s\u7917 a l\u7841 i ch\u259 n, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh tr\uc0\u259 ng tr\u7855 ng x\'e1m, ng\u7911  chung v\u7899 i qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7845 t s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 t\u7881 nh, nh\u7865  ch\'e2n nh\u7865  tay xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7915  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y: "Sao v\u7853 y? L\u7841 i ph\u7843 i \u273 i t\u259 ng ca?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'e2ng," Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u7845 p \'fang \u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t c\'e2u, "V\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  h\'f4m qua v\u7851 n ch\u432 a gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t xong."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "A Di\'ean, em l\u7845 y qu\u7847 n \'e1o t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y cho t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c, m\u7903  t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o b\'ean tr\'e1i ra, c\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 b\'ean trong l\'e0 qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7853 u v\u7851 n gi\'fap h\u7855 n m\u7863 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t kh\u7855 c m\u7903  ng\u259 n t\u7911  ra c\u7853 u l\u7841 i ng\'e2y ng\u432 \u7901 i \'97\'97t\u7847 ng tr\'ean t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o l\'e0 t\u226 \u769 m \u273 \'ea\u803 m c\u7853 u c\u7845 t, nh\u432 ng ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i ch\u7895  treo qu\u7847 n \'e1o l\u7841 i ch\u7891 ng ch\u7845 t t\'e1n lo\u7841 n m\u7845 y m\'f3n \u273 \u7891  linh tinh v\'e0 qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u361  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, n\'e0o c\'f3 qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, qu\u7847 n \'e1o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  s\u7907  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 t\u7871  ph\u7849 m \'e2m ph\u7911 , c\u7853 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng, trong t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng thanh t\u7881 nh b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y hay \u273 \u7909 ng v\'e0o t\u7871  ph\u7849 m c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  m\u7903  c\u7917 a t\u7911  c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901  t\u7841 i \u273 \'f3, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn nam nh\'e2n ph\'eda sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7853 m r\'e3i t\u7899 i g\u7847 n, m\u7897 t tay \'f4m eo c\u7853 u, m\u7897 t tay t\u7915  tr\'ean vai v\'f2ng qua \'f4m ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u, c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ch\u7863 t ch\u7869  k\u7873  nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915 ng c\'e1i h\'f4n m\'fat ho\u259 \u803 c nhe\u803  ho\u7863 c n\u7863 ng r\u417 i tr\'ean g\'e1y c\u7853 u, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau th\'e2n m\u7853 t t\'e1n t\u7881 nh, la\u803 i nh\u432  lo\'e0i th\'fa \u273 \'f9a gi\u7905 n con m\u7891 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thanh \'e2m tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p v\u7851 n mang theo \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7843 o b\u7889 i, h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac tr\u7903  l\u7841 i em \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra r\u7891 i ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong m\uc0\u7897 t s\'e1t na th\u7853 m ch\'ed \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean th\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong t\uc0\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o kh\u7843 m m\u7897 t t\u7845 m g\u432 \u417 ng l\u7899 n ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u r\'f5 r\'e0ng t\u432  th\u7871  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'fac n\'e0y, c\u361 ng l\'e0m cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng th\'e2n h\'ecnh c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c c\'f9ng g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t t\'e1i nh\u7907 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u y\'ean l\u7863 ng m\u7897 t gi\'e2y, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  linh quang hi\u7879 n ra nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n hai t\u7845 m ph\'f9 b\u7843 o m\u7879 nh h\'f4m qua \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n \u273 \u432 a cho m\'ecnh, l\u7845 y t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  nhanh nh\u7845 t r\'fat ra t\u7915  trong t\'fai \'e1o, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7845 t m\u7841 ng \u7845 n l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u361 ng th\u7915 a c\u417  tr\'e1nh tho\'e1t \'f4m \u7845 p c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t ch\u7841 y lo\u7841 n ra kh\u7887 i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , tay run r\u7849 y hai c\'e1i m\u7899 i v\u7863 n m\u7903  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f3a c\u7917 a, ra \u273 \u7871 n c\u7917 a nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n b\'ecnh s\u7913  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, gi\u7853 t m\u7841 nh xu\u7889 ng n\'e9m v\'e0o trong nh\'e0, t\u7921 a nh\u432  b\u7883  \'e1c qu\u7927  \u273 u\u7893 i theo ch\u7841 y nh\u432  \u273 i\'ean xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi thu\u7853 n tay v\'f2 ph\'f9 ch\'fa Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7845 n tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n, m\u7863 t tr\u7847 m nh\u432  n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7917 a nh\'e0 m\u7903  r\u7897 ng, th\'ec th\'e0o m\u7897 t c\'e2u "T\u7915  khi n\'e0o l\u7841 i th\'eam t\u7853 t x\u7845 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a r\u7891 i", ti\u7871 n l\'ean \u273 em to\'e0n b\u7897  c\u7917 a ch\'ednh c\u7917 a ch\u7889 ng tr\u7897 m nh\'e0 m\'ecnh \u273 \'f3ng k\u7929 , th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u v\u7915 a v\u7863 n tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  b\u7883  n\'e9m tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ecnh s\uc0\u7913  n\'e0y r\u7845 t ch\u7855 c, c\'f3 l\u7869  b\u7903 i kh\u7843  n\u259 ng ch\u7883 u l\u7921 c, b\u7883  n\'e9m nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\u7851 n nguy\'ean v\u7865 n kh\'f4ng t\u7893 n hao g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7847 m m\u7863 t khom l\u432 ng nh\u7863 t l\'ean n\u7855 m trong tay, m\u7863 t tr\'ean truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  \'e2m \u7845 m, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  v\u7851 n c\'f2n mang theo nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi ch\uc0\u7841 y ra c\u7917 a \u273 \u417 n nguy\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\'e1i xe, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u qu\'e1 ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t s\u7907  h\'e3i, \u7903  trong xe d\'f9 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i ma qu\u7927  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i th\'ec c\u361 ng lo l\u7855 ng trong t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng ho\u7843 ng lo\u7841 n n\'e0y s\u7869  g\'e2y ra tai n\u7841 n giao th\'f4ng. C\u7853 u ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng ra c\u7893 ng ti\u7875 u khu, \u273 \u7913 ng tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i m\u7899 i d\'e3n ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra... ng\'e0y h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra r\u7891 i...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi so v\u7899 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  qu\'e1i c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i c\'f2n \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  h\u417 n, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n xung quanh c\u7853 u, tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p \'e1c \'fd v\'e0 o\'e1n \u273 \u7897 c mu\u7889 n m\u432 u h\u7841 i c\u7853 u, k\'e9o c\u7853 u l\'e0m th\u7871  th\'e2n cho qu\u7927 , b\u7903 i v\'ec h\u7855 n v\u7851 n gi\u7919  l\u7841 i s\'e1ng su\u7889 t l\'fac l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i, x\u7843 o tr\'e1 v\'e0 b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng thanh s\u7855 c \'97\'97 m\'e0 d\'f9 l\'e0 l\'fac l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\u7893 i ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7895  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  xem nh\u432  l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng khu bu\'f4n b\'e1n, giao th\'f4ng thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n. C\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 c\'f3 hai chi\u7871 c xe bus c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  c\'e1ch nh\'e0 \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng xa, s\u7901  s\u7901  t\'fai qu\u7847 n, may m\'e0 b\'ean trong v\u7851 n c\'f2n ti\u7873 n l\u7867  ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua mua th\u7913 c \u259 n c\'f2n th\u7915 a l\u7841 i, ng\u7891 i xe bus nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'e0 \u273 \u7911  r\u7891 i. Ng\'e0y ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y xe bus c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 chen ch\'fac, \u273 i\u7875 m t\u7889 t l\'e0 nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i, d\u7891 i d\'e0o ng\u7853 p tr\'e0n sinh kh\'ed.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7883  Qu\u7871  h\'f4m nay ngh\u7881 , trong bi\u7879 t th\u7921  ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n \u7903  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, \'f4ng m\u7903  c\u7917 a \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o, qua b\u7897  d\u7841 ng v\'e0 s\u7855 c m\u7863 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, ph\'e1n \u273 o\'e1n n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng th\'e0nh c\'f4ng? Th\u7913  kia v\u7851 n s\u7889 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u7847 m m\u7863 c g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 c d\'f9 m\u7897 t kh\u7855 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o c\u7917 a \u273 \'e3 d\u7921  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u432 \u7899 c, nh\u432 ng sau khi nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1p \'e1n kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n v\u7851 n thay \u273 \u7893 i s\u7855 c m\u7863 t. \'d4ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\u297  ng\u7907 i lung tung, \'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\'f9 tr\u7845 n ma kh\'f4ng c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t nguy\'ean nh\'e2n \'97\'97 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7881  m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9 tr\u7845 n ma l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7845 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda ng\u7921 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ch\'fa \'fd th\u7845 y b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a, v\'ec v\u7853 y kho\'e1t tay \'e1o, d\u7851 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'ean l\u7847 u, ch\u7881  v\'e0o m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch c\'f3 ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m n\'f3i: "Vi\u7879 c n\'e0y c\'f2n c\u7847 n b\'e0n b\u7841 c k\u7929  h\u417 n, tr\u432 \u7899 c h\u7871 t c\u7853 u ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, n\u7871 u thi\u7871 u g\'ec th\'ec ng\'e0y mai ta k\'eau ch\u7883  Qu\u7871  mang t\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe ra \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'fd c\u7911 a \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia l\'e0 vi\u7879 c n\'e0y h\'f4m nay t\u7841 m th\u7901 i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u \u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y. H\'f4m nay chuy\u7879 n v\u7873  nh\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'ean, \u7903  ch\u7895  kh\'e1c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng \u7903  g\u7847 n cao nh\'e2n an to\'e0n h\u417 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7899  ra m\'ecnh c\'f2n ch\u432 a r\u7917 a m\u7863 t \u273 \'e3 ch\u7841 y \u273 i, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 ch\'fat x\u7845 u h\u7893 , v\u7897 i v\'e0ng n\'f3i c\'e1m \u417 n v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m nay t\'ednh m\uc0\u7841 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f3 b\u7843 o to\'e0n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh ng\'e0y mai s\u7869  xin ngh\u7881  ph\'e9p v\u7899 i \u273 \u417 n v\u7883 , ch\u7901  vi\u7879 c n\'e0y gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t xong th\'ec \u273 i l\'e0m tr\u7903  l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean hai tay tr\uc0\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7841 y kh\u7887 i nh\'e0, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i m\u432 \u7907 n \u273 \u7891  cho kh\'e1ch trong bi\u7879 t th\u7921  t\u7855 m r\u7917 a qua loa, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng l\u7901 i m\u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7885 c s\'e1ch c\u7911 a \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia, k\u7875  l\u7841 i k\u7929  c\'e0ng \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n l\'fac c\'f2n s\u7889 ng sau khi ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f9ng v\u7899 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c l\'e0m c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n x\u7845 u h\u7893  chuy\u7879 n n\'f3i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i v\u7873  t\'ecnh s\u7921  th\'e2n m\u7853 t m\'e0 t\u432  m\u7853 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, v\'ec v\u7853 y ch\u7881  \'fap \'fap m\u7903  m\u7903  di\u7877 n gi\u7843 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  \'e1m v\'e0 \u273 o\u7841 n th\u7901 i gian Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7909 y trang th\'e0nh th\'e2n ph\u7853 n b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u7903  chung v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, c\u7843 m t\'ecnh r\u7845 t t\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n nghe xong b\'e0y t\u7887  \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u, nh\u432 ng \'f4ng mu\u7889 n chu\u7849 n b\u7883  s\u7899 m m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ba ng\'e0y sau s\u7869  c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u273 i gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t vi\u7879 c n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i t\u7841 m th\u7901 i \u273 \'e8 xu\u7889 ng n\u7895 i lo s\u7907  tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p, \u7903  l\u7841 i ch\u7895  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'eam \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7853 u tr\u7857 n tr\u7885 c, g\u7847 n nh\u432  tr\u7855 ng \u273 \'eam kh\'f3 ng\u7911 , c\u7843  \u273 \'eam lo l\u7855 ng s\u7907  h\'e3i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o ti\'ean sinh c\'f3 b\u7889  tr\'ed g\'ec trong ph\'f2ng hay kh\'f4ng, \u273 \'fang l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam v\'f4 s\u7921 .\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng s\uc0\u7899 m h\'f4m sau ch\u7883  Qu\u7871  t\u7899 i d\u7885 n d\u7865 p nh\'e0 c\u7917 a \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\'e0m \u273 i\u7875 m t\'e2m, sau khi l\'e0m c\u417 m chi\u7873 u thu d\u7885 n xong xu\'f4i m\u7899 i r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i. \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m s\'e1ng tr\u432 a t\u7889 i m\u7899 i xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n c\u417 m, th\u7901 i gian c\'f2n l\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u t\u7921  giam m\'ecnh trong ph\'f2ng s\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e3 tr\u7843 i qua m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam b\'ecnh an, \u273 \'eam nay Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng lo l\u7855 ng b\u7845 t an gi\u7889 ng h\'f4m qua n\u7919 a, y\'ean l\u7863 ng \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch d\'f9ng m\'e1y t\'ednh \u273 \u7875  b\'e0n \u273 \u7885 c tin t\u7913 c tr\'ean m\u7841 ng \'97\'97 l\'fac c\u7853 u \u273 i kh\'f4ng mang theo \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, ngay c\u7843  xin ngh\u7881  ph\'e9p c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u432 \u7907 n \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i trong bi\u7879 t th\u7921  d\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nghe th\u7845 y m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7921 c k\u7923  vang c\u7911 a v\u7853 t n\u7863 ng r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t\'97\'97 l\'e0 t\u7915  ph\'f2ng s\'e1ch \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n. Hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  trong bi\u7879 t th\u7921  qu\u7843  th\u7921 c ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\'f3 d\u7921  c\u7843 m kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, c\u7853 u v\u7915 a ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng s\'e1ch c\u7911 a \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o v\u7915 a t\u7921  an \u7911 i m\'ecnh, ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0 l\u7899 n tu\u7893 i tay ch\'e2n kh\'f4ng nhanh nh\u7865 n, ch\u7855 c ch\u7881  l\'e0 l\u7905  tay \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i g\'ec \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7917 a ph\'f2ng s\'e1ch kh\'f4ng kh\'f3a, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7845 n l\'ean tay n\u7855 m \u273 \u7849 y c\'e1nh c\u7917 a g\u7895  m\'e0u n\'e2u ra, c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng b\'ean trong l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\'e0m c\u7853 u s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 n th\'eam m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, con ng\u432 \u417 i c\u361 ng v\'f4 th\u7913 c m\u7903  l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  th\u7845 y \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n m\u7863 t ngh\u7865 n \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng, hai m\u7855 t tr\u7907 n tr\u7915 ng, t\u7921 a h\u7891  b\u7883  m\u7897 t s\u7907 i d\'e2y th\u7915 ng v\'f4 h\'ecnh si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t. Tay \'f4ng \u273 \u7875  tr\'ean c\u7893  gi\'e3y d\u7909 a mu\u7889 n gi\u7857 ng ra, nh\u432 ng v\'f4 \'edch. Chi\u7871 c gh\u7871  g\u7895  \'f4ng hay ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7893  \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean, ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n l\'e0 l\'fac \u273 \u7893  xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t ph\'e1t ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay v\'f4 h\'ecnh \u273 \u7849 y l\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, c\'e1nh c\u7917 a g\u7895  m\'e0u n\'e2u ph\'eda sau c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n gi\'f3 l\u7841 nh kh\u7869  l\u432 \u7899 t qua, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, b\'ean tai vang l\'ean thanh \'e2m nh\u432  c\'f3 nh\u432  kh\'f4ng, nh\u7865  nh\u432  c\u417 n gi\'f3 nh\u7887 : "V\'ec sao kh\'f4ng v\u7873  nh\'e0, t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7907 i em c\u7843  \u273 \'eam..."\cb1 \
