\cb3 Tay \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n v\u7851 n v\'f4 th\u7913 c gi\u7857 ng co, nh\u432 ng kh\'ed l\u7921 c c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng y\u7871 u, m\u7855 t th\u7845 y \u273 \'e3 h\'edt v\'e0o nhi\u7873 u m\'e0 th\u7903  ra kh\'f4ng bao nhi\'eau r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\'fa \'fd th\uc0\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i v\'e0o, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng v\u432 \u417 n tay v\u7899 i v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, c\u7893  h\u7885 ng ph\'e1t ra thanh \'e2m "\'d4i \'f4i", tr\'ean m\u7863 t hi\u7879 n l\'ean m\u7897 t tia bi thi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng ti\u7871 n l\'ean hai b\u432 \u7899 c, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e0m g\'ec \'97\'97 tr\'ean c\u7893  h\u7885 ng \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec, \'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  kh\'f4ng kh\'ed si\u7871 t ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'ed t\u7913 c l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o b\'ean c\u7841 nh, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t c\'f3 m\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" \u273 i theo m\'ecnh, th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\u7869  run r\u7849 y. C\u7853 u \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 ai.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u417 i th\u7903  l\u7841 nh bu\u7889 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n d\u7847 n d\u7847 n v\'f4 l\u7921 c r\u361  xu\u7889 ng, h\'f4 h\u7845 p c\u361 ng c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng y\u7871 u, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7855 t v\u7851 n lu\'f4n nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ti\u7871 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, m\u7855 t th\u7845 y m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'ec m\'ecnh m\'e0 sinh m\u7879 nh li\'ean t\u7909 c x\'f3i m\'f2n trong khi b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 i b\u7845 t l\u7921 c ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u417  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y d\u7891 n \'e9p c\u7853 u g\u7847 n nh\u432  mu\u7889 n tan v\u7905 . C\u7853 u c\u7913 ng r\u7855 n ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905 , n\u432 \u417 ng theo c\u7843 m gi\'e1c quay sang "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\'ean c\u7841 nh, th\u7853 m ch\'ed v\u432 \u417 n tay ra th\u7917  k\'e9o tay h\u7855 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia \u7903  nh\'e0 c\u7853 u c\u7889  \'fd l\u7845 y l\'f2ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac h\u7855 n t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u cho r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh s\u7869  ch\u7881  ch\u7841 m v\'e0o kh\'f4ng kh\'ed, c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i \u273 \u7909 ng t\u7899 i th\'e2n th\u7875  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y h\u7855 n, l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u ch\u7841 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i c\'e2u n\'f3i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ti\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\'e0i c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'ec sao kh\'f4ng v\uc0\u7873  nh\'e0, t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7907 i em c\u7843  \u273 \'eam..."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u417  h\u7897 i s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia v\u7851 n \u273 ang nhanh ch\'f3ng tr\'f4i qua, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t tia kh\'ed t\u7913 c \u273 ang ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  cho \'f4ng, khi\u7871 n \'f4ng tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7845 p h\u7889 i v\'f9ng v\u7851 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915  sau khi b\u7887  \u273 i m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn n\u7919 a, nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i nh\'edch t\u7899 i g\u7847 n "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'e0m n\u361 ng nh\u7853 n sai t\'ecm ki\u7871 m \'f4m l\u7845 y eo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \'e1p ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh t\u7899 i, d\'ednh s\'e1t v\'e0o \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u432  th\u7871  th\'e2n m\u7853 t kh\u259 ng kh\'edt, n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t trong l\'fac v\'f4 th\u7913 c l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t \'97\'97 c\'f3 kinh, c\'f3 s\u7907 , c\'f3 ho\u7843 ng, c\'f3 s\u7847 u, ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'fac \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng c\u7921 c h\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \'f4m ch\u7863 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, ngh\u7865 n ng\'e0o c\u7847 u kh\u7849 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, anh th\u7843  \'f4ng \u7845 y \u273 i, c\u7847 u xin anh th\u7843  \'f4ng \u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng... T\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 l\u7895 i c\u7911 a em, \u273 \u7915 ng li\'ean l\u7909 y ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c. Ch\'fang ta v\u7873  nh\'e0, ch\'fang ta v\u7873  nh\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng. Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7847 u xin anh..."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i n\u259 ng l\u7897 n x\u7897 n, \u273 \u7841 i n\'e3o ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p, t\u7921  m\'ecnh n\'f3i ra b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m nh\u7919 ng g\'ec, ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng c\u7847 u xin, v\u7883 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u7889  g\u7855 ng d\'f9ng m\'f4i c\'f2n d\'ednh n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng h\'f4n c\u7893  v\'e0 hai m\'e1 l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ngay c\u7843  l\u7901 i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ho\'e0n ch\u7881 nh, trong mi\u7879 ng ch\u7881  nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng th\'ec th\'e0o g\u7885 i t\'ean h\u7855 n, l\u7863 p \u273 i l\u7863 p l\u7841 i ngh\u7865 n ng\'e0o "Ngh\'eanh Chi" "Xin anh" "V\u7873  nh\'e0" .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t qua bao l\'e2u, d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng th\u7847 n kinh k\'e9o c\u259 ng c\u7921 c \u273 \u7897 , c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\u7899 i th\u7901 i gian \u273 \'e3 m\u417  h\u7891 . C\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" b\'ean c\u7841 nh r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c nh\'fac nh\'edch, d\'e2y th\u7915 ng v\'f4 h\'ecnh si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t c\u7893  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean bu\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n ng\u7891 i b\u7879 t d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u432  c\'e1i b\u7877  h\u7887 ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u li\'ean t\u7909 c ho khan th\u7903  d\u7889 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngay sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay \'f4m eo c\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  h\u417 i c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n v\'e0nh tai c\u7853 u, thanh \'e2m tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p: "Nh\u7899  gi\u7919  l\u7901 i, t\'f4i \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\u7901  em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 b\'e0n tay kia bu\'f4ng ra, h\u7871 t th\u7843 y c\u361 ng b\u7895 ng ch\u7889 c y\'ean l\u7863 ng tr\u7903  l\u7841 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7845 t h\u7871 t s\u7913 c l\u7921 c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\u7885 i th\u7913  xung quanh m\u7901  m\u7883 t, ch\u7881  c\'f3 b\'ean tai v\'e0 h\'f4ng c\'f2n l\u7901  m\u7901  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o m\u417  h\u7891 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'fac h\u7855 n im h\u417 i l\u7863 ng ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a c\u432 \u7899 p m\u7897 t m\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7841 nh \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia \u273 \u7905  \'f4ng ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, v\u7895  l\u432 ng cho \'f4ng gi\'fap \'f4ng th\u7903  g\u7845 p \u273 i\u7873 u kh\'ed. Qua m\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n m\u7899 i h\'f2a ho\'e3n l\u7841 i, \'f4ng v\u7883 n c\'e1nh tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7853 m r\'e3i \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, th\u432 \u777  th\u432 \u777 , v\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361  n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ra l\u7901 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\'f9ng tay ra hi\u7879 u b\u7843 o c\u7853 u \u273 \u7905  m\'ecnh quay v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n c\'f3 m\'e1y \u273 \u7875  b\'e0n, b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t cu\u7889 n danh b\u7841  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i. \'d4ng t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\u7853 t m\u7897 t trang vi\u7871 t s\u7889  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a ch\u7883  Qu\u7871 , \'fd b\u7843 o Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i k\'eau b\'e0 t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, sau \u273 \'f3 xua xua tay v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\u7897  ra n\'e9t m\u7863 t bi ai t\u7921  tr\'e1ch, kh\'e0n gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u... \u273 i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o nh\'e2n ti\uc0\u7871 p t\u7909 c c\u7889  g\u7855 ng t\u7915  trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng t\u7855 c ngh\u7865 n ph\'e1t ra \'e2m thanh n\'f3i: "Th\u7853 t... xin l\u7895 i, t\u7841 m th\u7901 i... kh\'f4ng gi\'fap \u273 \u432 \u7907 c..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng ng\u259 n \'f4ng: "Ng\'e0i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n n\'f3i n\u7919 a. L\'e0 con c\'f3 l\u7895 i v\u7899 i ng\'e0i, li\'ean l\u7909 y ng\'e0i b\u7883  \u273 \u7841 i n\u7841 n n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n kho\'e1t tay \'e1o, kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7907 i t\u7899 i khi ch\u7883  Qu\u7871  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7899 i c\'e1o bi\u7879 t v\u7899 i \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n. L\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u nh\'ecn v\'f4 c\'f9ng tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh, t\u7921 a h\u7891  ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t m\u7845 t ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y xin gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i: "\u272 a t\u7841  ng\'e0i \u273 \'e3 gi\'fap con l\u7847 n n\'e0y. Con \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u r\'f5 r\u7891 i, tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y v\u7889 n l\'e0 con kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i m\'e0 l\u7845 y tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i m\'e0 l\u7845 y l\'e0 tr\u7897 m, hu\u7889 ng chi th\u7913  con tr\u7897 m c\'f2n l\'e0 tro c\u7889 t t\u432 \u7907 ng tr\u432 ng th\'e2n th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta. L\'e0 con thi\u7871 u n\u7907  h\u7855 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, l\u7847 n n\'e0y tr\u7903  v\u7873 , h\u7855 n b\u7855 t con tr\u7843  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, con s\u7869  \u273 em nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  ph\u7843 i tr\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7843  l\u7841 i. Thi\'ean l\'fd lu\'e2n h\u7891 i ch\'ednh l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7885 c ng\'e0i ph\'ed t\'e2m."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7841 i h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n b\'e1i m\u7897 t c\'e1i b\'e0y t\u7887  xin l\u7895 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 X\uc0\u7845 u nh\u7845 t c\'f9ng l\u7855 m l\'e0 l\u7845 y m\u7841 ng \u273 \u7873 n m\u7841 ng th\'f4i. C\u7853 u ngh\u297 , r\u361  m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n th\u7903  ph\'ec ph\'f2, nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\'ean t\u7909 c c\u7843 m t\u7841  m\'ecnh n\'f3i c\'e1o bi\u7879 t, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7919  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915  trong bi\u7879 t th\u7921  \u273 i ra \u273 \'e3 g\u7847 n m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901 , n\u417 i n\'e0y t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i xa, ch\u7881  th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng m\u7899 i c\'f3 xe ri\'eang l\'e1i tr\u7903  v\u7873 , ngay c\u7843  taxi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y. C\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mang \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, \'e1ng ch\u7915 ng th\u7901 i gian \u273 i nhanh v\'e0i b\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 u\u7893 i theo chuy\u7871 n xe bus cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 i g\u7847 n t\u7899 i tr\u7841 m xe bus xa xa \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 \u7853 u \u7903  ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3, xe \u7903  \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  v\u7873  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 i\u7875 m g\u7847 n nh\'e0, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn k\u7929 , nhanh ch\'f3ng ch\u7841 y ch\u7853 m hai b\u432 \u7899 c l\'ean xe b\u7887  ti\u7873 n v\'e0o th\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e1i xe m\uc0\u7855 t v\u7851 n lu\'f4n nh\'ecn ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u7853 u l\'ean xe c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, tr\'ean xe r\u7845 t tr\u7889 ng, tr\u7915  c\u7853 u ra ch\u7881  c\'f3 ba b\u7889 n h\'e0nh kh\'e1ch, ng\u7891 i ph\'e2n t\'e1n c\'e1c ch\u7895 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean qu\'e9t m\u7855 t m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i \u7903  \u273 u\'f4i xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7871 n xe cu\u7889 i th\u7901 i gian ch\u7901  h\u417 i l\'e2u m\u7897 t ch\'fat, hai ph\'fat sau khi c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng xe m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u l\u7855 c l\u432  kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gh\u7871  nh\'ecn quang c\u7843 nh th\'e0nh ph\u7889  m\u7897 t m\u7843 nh \u273 en k\u7883 t ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 . C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t sau khi v\u7873  nh\'e0 \u273 \u7907 i ch\u7901  m\'ecnh s\u7869  l\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t l\'e0, b\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u7841 y kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t, tr\u7889 n kh\'f4ng xong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'f4ng qua chuy\u7879 n h\'f4m nay \u273 \'e3 cho c\u7853 u th\u7845 y r\u7845 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng r\u7891 i, \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng ch\u7889 ng l\u7841 i h\u7855 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a m\u7845 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i m\u7841 ng. Nh\u7919 ng h\'f2a th\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7841 o s\u297  c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p t\u7915  nh\u7887  ngay c\u7843  b\u7843 o v\u7879  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng, hu\u7889 ng chi \u273 \u7889 i ph\'f3 v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 th\u7875  \'e1p ch\u7871  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i y\'eau t\'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  n\'e3y \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  l\'f2ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n n\u7863 ng n\u7873  ng\u7849 n ng\u417 , trong tay c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891  hay \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  xem th\u7901 i gian, ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t l\'e0 xe v\u7851 n lu\'f4n ch\u7841 y, ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  v\u7851 n t\u7889 i nh\u432  m\u7921 c, t\u7921 a h\u7891  v\u7851 n ch\u432 a r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i ph\u7909  c\u7853 n n\u417 i n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 qua bao l\'e2u. \u272 \u7897 t nhi\'ean sau khi \u273 \u7883 nh th\u7847 n l\u7841 i m\u7899 i ph\'e1t gi\'e1c b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng\'97\'97 \u273 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 xe bus, v\'ec sao qua l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n tr\u7841 m ti\u7871 p theo? V\u7851 n lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai mu\u7889 n l\'ean xe c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai mu\u7889 n xu\u7889 ng xe?\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi \'fd th\uc0\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y c\u7853 u li\u7873 n c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c l\'ean, t\u7841 m th\u7901 i d\u7857 n xu\u7889 ng n\u7895 i lo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  nh\'e0, \'e2m th\u7847 m ch\'fa \'fd b\'ean trong xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u7903  trong l\'f2ng y\'ean l\u7863 ng \u273 \u7871 m, kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m \u273 \u7871 m \u273 \u7871 n ba tr\u259 m, xe v\u7851 n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7863 n t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng qu\u7865 o r\u7869 , kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7893 i l\'e0n, kh\'f4ng l\u7855 c l\u432 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\'ean con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c xe n\'e0y \u273 ang ch\u7841 y. Th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng thay \u273 \u7893 i, v\u7851 n l\'e0 s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 m\u7883 t m\u7901  t\u7889 i \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c, xa xa m\u417  h\u7891  l\'f3e l\'ean \'e1nh s\'e1ng \u7843 m \u273 \u7841 m tr\u7855 ng nh\u7907 t kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7915  n\u417 i n\'e0o \u273 \u7871 n \'97\'97 l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n cho r\u7857 ng \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 \'e1nh s\'e1ng t\u7915  n\u7897 i th\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean si\uc0\u7871 t n\u7855 m tay, ch\'fa \'fd nh\'ecn m\u7845 y h\'e0nh kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c. L\'fac l\'ean xe trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n l\u7841 i s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y, vi\u7879 c trong l\'fac ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t b\u7887  qua \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y ho\'e0n to\'e0n gi\u7889 ng v\u7899 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'ea t\'e2m, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u c\'f2n c\'f3 b\u7889 n v\u7883  kh\'e1ch, th\'eam l\'e1i xe t\u7893 ng c\u7897 ng n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i, to\'e0n b\u7897  \u259 n m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o d\'e0i \u273 \u7853 m m\'e0u, tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c ng\u7891 i th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7901 , kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  gi\u7889 ng \u273 a s\u7889  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng tr\'ean xe bus s\u7869  c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xem \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh s\'e1ng \uc0\u273 \'e8n ch\'e2n kh\'f4ng tr\'ean tr\u7847 n xe tr\u7855 ng nh\u7907 t, d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n chi\u7871 u xu\u7889 ng, b\u7885 n h\u7885  to\'e0n b\u7897  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\'f3ng.\cb1 \
