\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn v\uc0\u7873  ph\'eda m\u7897 t h\'e0nh kh\'e1ch ng\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u hai h\'e0ng, c\u7917 a s\u7893  xe ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u m\u7863 t h\u7855 n \'97\'97 t\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7841 o t\u7847 m th\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta sau khi nh\'ecn qua s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nh\u7899 , bi\u7875 u l\u7897  c\u7913 ng nh\u7855 c, m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t nh\'ecn ch\u259 m ch\u259 m ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t to\'e0n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7893 i da g\'e0, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n, t\'ean h\'e0nh kh\'e1ch kia kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 ang nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 , m\'e0 l\'e0 v\u7851 n lu\'f4n th\'f4ng qua ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u c\u7911 a c\u7917 a s\u7893  nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i ph\'eda sau!\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c s\u7901  l\'ean ng\u7921 c, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng s\u7901  th\u7845 y g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tro c\uc0\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac kinh s\u7907  \u273 \'e3 n\'e9m \u273 i, linh ng\u7885 c c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o ti\'ean sinh b\u7883  c\u7853 u li\'ean l\u7909 y \u273 \u7871 n thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a b\u7887  n\u7917 a c\'e1i m\u7841 ng, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p chu\u7849 n b\u7883  th\u7913  g\'ec h\u7897  m\u7879 nh l\'fac c\u7853 u \u273 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng n\'ean \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 cao v\u7853 n kh\'ed c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, l\u7845 y th\u7875  ch\u7845 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, c\u7913  th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 \'eam h\'f4m khuya kho\u7855 t \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i xe ma c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 g\'ec l\u7841 . Th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c \u7903  b\'ean Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n, khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u trong th\u7901 i gian m\u7897 t n\u259 m n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c m\u7845 t \u273 i t\'e2m ph\'f2ng b\u7883  khi x\u432 a; hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  t\'e2m tr\'ed c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  nh\'e0 kia chi\u7871 m l\u7845 y, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng m\u7845 y ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  n\'e0y n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i l\'ean xe ma, lo\u7841 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  ch\u7841 y tho\'e1t. Kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i c\'f2n ch\u432 a tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7863 p Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, tr\'e1i l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 ph\u7843 i ch\u7871 t \u7903  \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i ho\uc0\u7843 ng s\u7907 , c\u7853 u v\u7853 y m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 ch\'fat m\u7845 t m\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng l\'e0 ch\u7871 t, c\u7853 u ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i th\'e0 ch\u7871 t trong tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7853 t c\'f3 l\u7895 i, nu\u7889 t l\u7901 i r\u7891 i." C\u7853 u l\u7849 m nh\u7849 m d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7853 t gi\u7853 t kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng, n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t tia kh\u7893  \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y, xe ng\u7915 ng, c\u7917 a xe m\u7903  ra, gi\'f3 \u273 \'eam tho\'e1ng c\'e1i \'f9a v\'e0o, th\u7893 i tan kh\'f4ng kh\'ed tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c \u7911  d\u7897 t trong xe l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kinh ng\uc0\u7841 c nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7917 a xe, l\u7841 i ch\u7881  \'e2m th\u7847 m n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t quy\u7873 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\'f9y ti\u7879 n \u273 i qua \u273 \'f3 \'97\'97 ai bi\u7871 t ngo\'e0i kia l\'e0 nh\'e2n gian hay l\'e0 \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c, ai bi\u7871 t l\'ean xe l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i hay l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\'e0nh kh\'e1ch" trong xe c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u432 \u7899 c l\'ean xe. H\u7855 n m\u7863 c \'e1o s\u417 mi ng\u7855 n tay v\'e0 qu\u7847 n t\'e2y d\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921  ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i l\'e0m \u273 \'eam, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng hai tay tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, phong th\'e1i nh\'e0n h\u7841 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fat m\u7879 t m\u7887 i sau m\u7897 t ng\'e0y l\'e0m vi\u7879 c n\'e0o c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng. L\u7841 i th\'eam t\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7841 o xu\u7845 t ch\'fang kh\'ed ch\u7845 t phi ph\'e0m, v\u7915 a nh\'ecn li\u7873 n bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n tuy\u7879 t kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u417 \u768 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn h\uc0\u7855 n, \u273 \'fang l\'e0 b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng n\u7855 m tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u t\'e2m tr\u7841 ng c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng, kinh ho\u7843 ng, s\u7907  h\'e3i, l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y v\u7853 y m\'e0 t\u7915  \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng th\u7903  ph\'e0o nh\u7865  nh\'f5m. T\u7921 a h\u7891  chi\u7871 c xe ma n\'e0y, t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh qu\u7927  d\u7883  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 y m\'e0 trong v\'f4 th\u7913 c ho\'e0n to\'e0n qu\'ean m\u7845 t \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i l\'e0 \'e1c qu\u7927  l\u7899 n nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t ch\u7919  "Di\u7879 p" ng\u259 n \u7903  trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7915 ng to m\u7855 t nh\'ecn nam nh\'e2n t\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng gh\u7871  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n v\'e0 nh\u7919 ng "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" kh\'e1c tr\'ean xe n\'e0y gi\u7889 ng nhau, \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\'f3ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i: "Sao anh l\u7841 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e3 tr\u7877  nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\'e0 em v\u7851 n ch\u432 a v\u7873  nh\'e0, t\'f4i \u273 i \u273 \'f3n em. N\u7871 u kh\'f4ng em b\u7883  b\u7855 t c\'f3c th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i r\u7845 t t\u7921  nhi\'ean, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7891 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec v\u7907  v\u7873  mu\u7897 n m\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i: "Th\u7901 i gian l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\'e0 em ch\u432 a tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, t\'f4i c\'f2n t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng em l\u7841 i \u273 \u7893 i \'fd r\u7891 i, ai ng\u7901  em v\u7853 y m\'e0 ng\u7889 c \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i l\'ean nh\u7847 m xe." H\u7855 n n\'f3i xong nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \'e1nh m\u7855 t cong l\'ean kh\u7869  n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, t\u7921 a nh\u432  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7851 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i t\'ecnh nh\'e2n, \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng ph\'e1t sinh qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m h\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y lu\'f4n lu\'f4n c\'f3 m\u7883  l\u7921 c kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t, th\'e0nh qu\u7927  c\u361 ng c\'f2n \u273 \u7865 p m\u7855 t h\u417 n c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn h\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe v\uc0\u7851 n y\'ean l\u7863 ng ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 \'e8n ch\'e2n kh\'f4ng tr\'ean tr\u7847 n v\u7851 n tr\u7855 ng nh\u7907 t, h\'e0nh kh\'e1ch ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u432  th\u7871  ng\u7891 i v\u7851 n c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c, ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 v\u7851 n d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u273 \u7875  \'fd nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng th\'e8m \uc0\u273 \u7875  \'fd ch\'fat n\'e0o, b\u7903 i v\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \u7903  b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi..." C\u7853 u h\'e1 m\u7891 m mu\u7889 n n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7891 i l\u7841 i du\u7895 i ng\'f3n tr\u7887  tay ph\u7843 i d\'e1n l\'ean m\'f4i c\u7853 u ng\u259 n tr\u7903  l\u7901 i c\u7853 u ch\u432 a xong, tay tr\'e1i n\u7855 m tay c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac n\'e0y m\uc0\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 th\u7901 i gian m\u7897 t c\'e2u n\'f3i, xe kia trong l\'fac c\u7853 u ch\u432 a ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 ng\u7915 ng l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, c\u7917 a sau m\u7903  ra. H\'e0nh kh\'e1ch kh\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u v\u7851 n b\u7845 t \u273 \'f4\u803 ng nh\u432  c\u361 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'e9o c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i xe l\'e0 khu r\uc0\u432 \u768 ng nho\u777  trong c\'f4ng vi\'ean c\'e1ch nh\'e0 c\u7853 u hai con ph\u7889 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 tr\u7841 m xe bus k\u7923  di\u7879 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'e9o c\u7853 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i h\u432 \u7899 ng v\'e0o trong r\u7915 ng c\'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, " Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c ngh\u7865 n xu\u7845 t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t c\'e2u, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n t\u7915 ng ch\'fat m\u7897 t m\'e0 nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, "... Anh mu\u7889 n \u259 n em sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i v\u7873  truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t \'e1c qu\u7927  \u259 n th\u7883 t ng\u432 \u7901 i. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432  v\u7853 y, kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  qu\'e1i kia t\'ecm k\u7867  th\u7871  th\'e2n. M\'ecnh c\u7847 m tro c\u7889 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i ch\u7881  c\'f3 mang h\u7871 t m\'e1u th\u7883 t to\'e0n b\u7897  tr\u7843  cho h\u7855 n m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7843  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'f3n n\u7907  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean cho l\'e0 h\uc0\u7855 n ng\u7847 m th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n, do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng kh\u7849 n c\u7847 u n\'f3i: "... \u272 \u7915 ng \u259 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng, v\u7873  nh\'e0 l\u7841 i \u259 n?"\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 c d\'f9 l\'e0 c\u7853 u sai tr\u432 \u7899 c, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n tham lam m\'e0 mu\u7889 n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n, mu\u7889 n gi\u7919  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t tia th\u7875  di\u7879 n, kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n ph\u417 i th\'e2y n\u417 i \u273 \u7891 ng kh\'f4ng m\'f4ng qu\u7841 nh n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'e2n Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi chuy\u7875 n h\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7897 t v\'f2ng, d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, v\u7873  nh\'e0 l\u7841 i \u259 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh ban \u273 \u7847 u c\u7911 a h\u7855 n v\u7889 n l\'e0 mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i d\u7841 o c\'f4ng vi\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi v\uc0\u7873  nh\'e0 nh\'ecn \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891  m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 m\u7897 t gi\u7901  s\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi v\'e0o c\uc0\u7917 a v\u7851 n n\u417 m n\u7899 p lo s\u7907  nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \'e1c qu\u7927  s\u7869  \u259 n th\u7883 t ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u259 n t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u, l\'e0 \u259 n s\u7889 ng hay gi\u7871 t ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i m\u7899 i \u259 n, m\'ecnh li\u7879 u c\'f3 \u273 au hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "\u272 i r\u7917 a m\u7863 t \u273 i, \u273 \u7913 ng ng\u7889 c \u7903  \u273 \u7845 y l\'e0m g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean "A" m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng theo m\u7879 nh l\u7879 nh \u273 i r\u7917 a m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'eau c\u7853 u l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n th\'e0nh th\u7853 t ng\u7891 i l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, vu\u7889 t ga gi\u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0ng nh\u7841 t th\u7845 t th\u7847 n ngh\u297 , n\u7871 u m\'ecnh b\u7883  x\u7867  ra \u259 n \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y li\u7879 u c\'f3 l\'e0m d\u417  ga gi\u432 \u7901 ng hay kh\'f4ng, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 b\u7897  ga gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u r\u7845 t th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i theo t\u7899 i, l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u361 ng l\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7911  \u7845 n c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong ch\u259 n, t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi?" C\u7853 u g\u7885 i t\'ean h\u7855 n, trong \u273 \'eam khuya y\'ean t\u297 nh nghe \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t m\u7873 m m\u7841 i, c\'f2n mang theo m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\'fang t\'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u7911  \u273 i, h\'f4m nay kh\'f4ng \u259 n em n\u7919 a, mu\u7897 n r\u7891 i, ng\'e0y mai em v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i \u273 i l\'e0m kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i sao. Kh\'f4ng v\u7897 i, ng\'e0y mai l\u7841 i \u259 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7911  c\'f3 ch\'fat bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i. R\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\'ecnh li\u7873 n s\u7907  mu\u7889 n ch\u7871 t, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  n\u7857 m c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7911  say s\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ho\'e0n to\'e0n tho\uc0\u7843 i m\'e1i, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi b\u7883  m\'f9i th\u417 m b\u7919 a s\'e1ng l\'e0m t\u7881 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi cong ng\'f3n tr\u7887  g\'f5 g\'e1y c\u7853 u, mang theo ch\'fat c\u7843 m gi\'e1c man m\'e1t: "D\u7853 y th\'f4i, b\u7843 y r\u432 \u7905 i r\u7891 i, \u273 i l\'e0m mu\u7897 n s\u7869  b\u7883  tr\u7915  l\u432 \u417 ng, ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n r\'f5 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 s\u7907  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi hay l\'e0 s\u7907  tr\u7915  l\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7841 nh gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o m\u7899 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7863 t s\u7841 ch l\'e0 ph\u7859 ng, b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7863 c m\u7845 y h\'f4m \u7903  ch\u7895  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7855 m gi\u7863 t thay m\u7899 i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  l\u7845 y \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u259 n s\'e1ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i chu\u7849 n b\u7883  s\u7861 n c\u7863 p \u273 i l\'e0m, b\'ean trong c\'f3 \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, t\'fai ti\u7873 n, ch\'eca kh\'f3a xe c\'e1c lo\u7841 i, m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  s\u7869  h\u7841  m\'ecnh l\'e0m c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c ph\u7909  t\'e1 cho m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u xoa xoa m\u361 i, \'f4m c\u7863 p ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gh\u7871  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  con v\u7853 t nh\u7887  nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. B\u7903 i v\'ec sau khi v\u7873  nh\'e0 t\'ecnh h\'ecnh ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n c\'f9ng v\u7899 i t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng nguy\'ean b\u7843 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'e1c nhau, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c n\'ean \u7913 ng \u273 \u7889 i th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tan t\uc0\u7847 m nh\u7899  mua th\u7913 c \u259 n v\u7873 , mua nhi\u7873 u rau m\u7897 t ch\'fat, kh\'f4ng n\'ean mua nguy\'ean th\u7883 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'e2ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nu\'f4i b\'e9o r\uc0\u7891 i \u259 n m\u7899 i ngon."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ng\uc0\u7889 c \u273 i ch\u259 ng n\u7919 a l\'fac n\'e0y c\u361 ng hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ngo\'e0i mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i "\u258 n" ch\u7881  l\'e0 thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i \u273 \u7875  l\u7915 a g\u7841 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng n\u7871 u ngay c\u7843  m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, ngay c\u7843  m\u7897 t th\'e2n huy\u7871 t nh\u7909 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u h\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n, c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  ngh\u297  kh\'f4ng ra Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean chuy\u7875 n ra ph\'eda sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \u273 \u432 a tay bu\u7897 c l\u7841 i th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u. Ng\'f3n tay h\u7855 n c\'f3 ch\'fat l\u7841 nh, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7901 i sinh th\'e2n th\u7875  l\u7841 nh, kh\'f4ng c\'f3ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e1, v\u7851 n trong ph\u7841 m vi ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n c\u7911 a c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\'f4 c\'f9ng quen thu\u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u bi\u7871 t \u7903  trong \u273 \u7921 ng tro c\u7889 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\u7847 n n\'e0y l\u7841 i l\'e0 ch\u7911  nh\'e2n t\u7921  tay \u273 em tro c\u7889 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 eo l\'ean cho c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i, gh\'e9 v\'e0o l\u7895  tai c\u7853 u phun kh\'ed n\'f3i: "L\u7847 n n\'e0y mang ch\u7855 c r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p l\u7841 i l\u7845 y xu\u7889 ng, l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng cho n\'e9m."\cb1 \
