\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai th\u7845 y h\'ecnh b\'f3ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u7903  trong m\u7855 t nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i v\'f2ng qua \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n, hai tay v\'f2ng xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i kho\'e1t l\'ean l\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n ch\'f3p m\u361 i c\u7853 u: "... Th\u7853 t xin l\u7895 i, t\'f4i sai r\u7891 i, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng n\'ean g\u7841 t em, d\'f9ng ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c \u273 \'f3 xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t em. L\'e0 t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 m\'ea t\'e2m em, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o n\'ean m\u7899 i l\'e0m nh\u432  v\u7853 y. T\'f4i ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\'edch ai, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o... Tr\'ean m\u7841 ng n\'f3i nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau nhau l\'fac h\u7865 n h\'f2 s\u7869  c\'f9ng nhau xem phim, \u273 i c\'f4ng vi\'ean t\u7843 n b\u7897 , sau n\'e0y t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i c\'f9ng em."\cb1 \
\cb3 "A Di\'ean, \uc0\u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907  t\'f4i. L\u7847 n n\'e0y h\'e3y th\u7917  d\'f9ng \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t c\u7911 a ch\'ednh em \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7899 i ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\'ec ra Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam h\'f4m qua d\u7851 n c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng xe \u7903  c\'f4ng vi\'ean l\'e0 mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i d\u7841 o.\cb1 \
