\cf2 \cb3 L\'e3o gia t\uc0\u7917  kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "H\u7891 ng nhan x\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4, m\u7863 t n\u7841  m\u7929  nh\'e2n. C\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7899 p da kia l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec, t\u7897 i g\'ec b\u7883  n\'f3 m\'ea ho\u7863 c u\u7893 ng h\u7841 i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u. Di\u7879 n m\u7841 o th\u7921 c th\u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u432 ng ra c\'f9ng v\u7899 i khi h\u7855 n c\'f2n s\u7889 ng gi\u7889 ng nhau nh\u432  \u273 \'fac, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh h\u7891  ly c\u7889  \'fd d\u7909  d\u7895  m\'ecnh, sao c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i m\'ecnh b\u7883  h\u7855 n m\'ea ho\u7863 c? H\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng h\u7841 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng bi\u7871 t ph\'e0m nh\'e2n c\'f2n d\u7877  d\'e0ng ph\'e1 v\u7905  l\u7901 i th\u7873 , n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \u7871 n l\u7901 i b\u7883 a \u273 \u7863 t c\u7911 a ma qu\u7927 , nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n th\u7917  tin t\u432 \u7903 ng h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7897 t \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n kh\'f4n c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7845 p m\'ea b\u7845 t ng\u7897 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n c\u7843 m k\'edch l\'e3o gia t\u7917  c\u7889  g\u7855 ng c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng m\'ecnh, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  m\'ecnh c\'e1o t\u7915  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
