\cb3 \'d4ng th\uc0\u7903  d\'e0i: "C\u7853 u ch\u7845 p m\'ea b\u7845 t h\u7889 i, ta \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u432 \u7905 ng c\u7847 u. Cho c\u7853 u \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7881  n\'e0y, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 s\u432  m\'f4n c\u7911 a ta, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\'f9y ti\u7879 n truy\u7873 n ra ngo\'e0i. B\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u t\'e0 kh\'ed nh\u7853 p th\u7875 , hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  s\u7907  lu\'e2n h\u7891 i chuy\u7875 n th\u7871  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ti\'eau tan h\u7871 t, c\'f3 khi c\'f2n d\u7851 n t\u7899 i y\'eau t\'e0, \u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  mang t\u7899 i x\'fai qu\u7849 y cho \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u b\'ean c\u7841 nh. N\u259 ng l\u7921 c ta c\'f3 h\u7841 n, \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y kh\'f4ng gi\'fap \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u, n\u7871 u c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian th\'ec \u273 \u7871 n s\u432  m\'f4n ta m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n, lo\u7841 i tr\u7915  nh\u7919 ng x\'fai qu\u7849 y kia \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean qu\uc0\u7843  th\u7921 c r\u7845 t s\u7907  li\'ean l\u7909 y \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c. Th\u7875  ch\u7845 t c\u7853 u tr\u7901 i sinh b\u7883  qu\u7927  qu\'e1i qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u, l\'fac n\'e0y ch\u7859 ng qua l\'e0 thay \u273 \u7893 i t\u7915  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c b\u7883  r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u th\u7913  r\'ecnh m\'f2 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh s\u7889 ng chung ch\u7881  v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e0 th\'f4i, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m l\u7901 i \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia n\'f3i t\'e0 kh\'ed nh\u7853 p th\u7875  li\'ean l\u7909 y ki\u7871 p sau c\'e1c lo\u7841 i huy\u7873 n di\u7879 u kh\'f3 gi\u7843 i th\'edch g\'ec \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u lo l\u7855 ng m\'ecnh v\'e0 qu\u7927  \u7903  chung nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\u7853 t s\u7921  s\u7869  mang \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 n xui cho ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7883 a ch\u7881  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia cho kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 xa, \u7903  ngay t\u7881 nh b\'ean c\u7841 nh, nh\u432 ng \u7849 n trong n\'fai c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  t\'ecm cho l\u7855 m, song b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n th\u7871  n\'e0o, th\u7901 i gian ba ng\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \u7911  \u273 i \u273 i v\u7873  v\u7873  m\u7897 t v\'f2ng r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873  k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u273 \u7889 i, ch\u7881  n\'f3i "Em mu\u7889 n \u273 i th\'ec \u273 i, t\'f4i \u273 i c\'f9ng em" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7921  \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 i v\'e0o cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n, l\u7841 i xin th\'eam m\u7897 t ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  n\u7919 a, l\'fac \u273 \u7863 t v\'e9 r\u7845 t do d\u7921 , kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 n\'ean mua v\'e9 cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi hay kh\'f4ng. Kh\'f4ng mua v\'e9 chung quy lu\'f4n c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ch\u7897 t d\u7841  tr\u7889 n v\'e9, v\u7899 i l\u7841 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i; n\u7871 u mua v\'e9 m\'e0 n\'f3i, nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c th\u7845 y gh\u7871  tr\u7889 ng, n\u7871 u \u273 \'f4ng ng\u432 \u7901 i thi\u7871 u ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng s\u7869  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i v\'e0o, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
