\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7917  th\u432 \u417 ng l\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, anh \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\u7901  em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? Em mang theo tro c\u7889 t, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd, vi\u7879 c n\'e0y \u273 \'e0nh t\u7841 m th\u7901 i g\'e1c l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7889 n \u273 ang l\u7847 n l\u7919 a, qua m\u7845 y ng\'e0y l\u7841 i ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p Ti\u7875 u V\u432 \u417 ng ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n m\'ecnh b\u7883  c\u7843 m n\u7863 ng n\u7857 m vi\u7879 n; L\'fd t\u7927  l\'e0m \u7903  t\u7893  c\'e1ch v\'e1ch v\u7915 a m\u7899 i ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c v\u7899 i c\u7853 u xong b\u7883  tr\u7853 t ch\'e2n l\'fac xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u; c\'f9ng v\u7899 i h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac tan l\'e0m g\u7863 p L\u432 u ca d\u7851 n theo con trai h\u7885 c ti\u7875 u h\u7885 c, c\u7853 u t\'f9y ti\u7879 n n\'f3i m\u7845 y c\'e2u v\u7899 i \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887 , h\'f4m nay \u273 i l\'e0m ch\u7907 t nghe L\u432 u ca than th\u7903  n\'f3i con trai m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng v\u432 \u7907 t qua k\'ec thi, ti\u7875 u h\u7885 c m\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2y... Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng c\'f3 ch\'fat lo l\u7855 ng l\'e0 m\'ecnh l\'e0m li\'ean l\u7909 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  d\'ednh v\u7853 n \u273 en.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 t n\u432 \u7899 c l\'e0m tr\'e0n ly cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\'e0 l\'fac n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i ch\'fa m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t tin m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\'fa v\u7853 y m\'e0 \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7883  cao huy\u7871 t \'e1p b\u7845 t t\u7881 nh \u7903  c\'f4ng ty. Trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ch\'fa v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'e0i gi\u7887 i th\'e2n th\u7875  kh\u7887 e m\u7841 nh, h\u7847 u nh\u432  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i, chuy\u7879 n sinh b\u7879 nh n\u7857 m vi\u7879 n c\u7921 c \'edt ph\'e1t sinh \u7903  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fa. Trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh v\u7851 n n\'f3i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec l\u7899 n, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 xu\u7845 t vi\u7879 n r\u7891 i, b\u7843 o c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n lo l\u7855 ng cho m\'ecnh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i th\u7847 m n\'f3i trong l\'f2ng, m\'ecnh v\'e0 ch\'fa tuy r\u7857 ng m\u7897 t n\u259 m ch\u7859 ng g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y l\u7847 n, nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 quan h\u7879  huy\u7871 t th\u7889 ng, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n x\'fai qu\u7849 y c\u361 ng \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n ch\'fa hay kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tu\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y chuy\u7879 n ph\u7843 i ho\'e0n th\'e0nh trong \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m, th\u7913  s\'e1u c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 xin ngh\u7881  chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 i s\u432  m\'f4n \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n.\cb1 \
