\cb3 V\'ec th\uc0\u7901 i gian \u273 ang g\u7845 p, chi\u7873 u th\u7913  n\u259 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t, \'e1ng ch\u7915 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901  \u273 \'eam c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i, ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m h\'f4m sau c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i t\'ecm ch\u7895  kia.\cb1 \
\
