\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u7871 t s\u7913 c nghi ho\u7863 c: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i anh kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e1i xe \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi "\'c0..." m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, n\'f3i: "Tuy l\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7857 ng l\'e1i xe, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n n\'f3 \u273 \'f4\u803 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean lo l\uc0\u7855 ng t\'e0i x\u7871  kh\'e1c trong l\'fac l\u417  \u273 \'e3ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y chi\u7871 c xe n\'e0y c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  sinh ra \'e1p l\u7921 c t\'e2m l\'fd, tuy r\u7857 ng c\u361 ng r\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e2m, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t \'fd t\u7889 t c\u7911 a Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i ra ngo\'e0i m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng \u273 \'f4i kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i qu\'e1 k\'ec qu\'e1i, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i l\'fac ngh\u7881  ch\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean mu\u7889 n m\u7897 t c\u259 n ph\'f2ng c\'f3 gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i theo c\u7853 u ti\u7871 n v\'e0o ph\'f2ng \u273 i v\'f2ng quanh, ng\u7891 i \u7903  b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng k\'e9o hai chi\u7871 c g\u7889 i \u273 \u7847 u s\'e1t v\'e0o gi\u7919 a, t\u7921 a h\u7891  r\u7845 t h\'e0i l\'f2ng v\u7899 i c\'e1ch s\u7855 p x\u7871 p n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m h\'f4m sau mua \u273 \u7891  \u259 n xong li\u7873 n d\u7921 a theo h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n l\'e1i xe \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7881  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia cho. Ch\u7841 y d\u7885 c theo \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'fai ngo\u7857 n ngo\'e8o c\u7843  bu\u7893 i, xe \u273 i t\u7899 i m\u7897 t th\'f4n tr\u432 \u7899 c sau \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i b\u7897 . H\u7887 i th\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i trong th\'f4n, c\'e1c th\'f4n d\'e2n c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i l\'ean n\'fai n\u7917 a gi\u7901  n\u7919 a c\'f3 m\u7897 t *qu\'e1n r\u7845 t l\u7899 n, c\u361 ng ch\u7881  h\u432 \u7899 ng cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (qu\'e1n: n\uc0\u417 i th\u7901  c\u7911 a c\'e1c \u273 \u7841 o s\u297 )
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia \u273 \'e3 gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u s\u417  qua s\u432  m\'f4n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh cho c\u7853 u, b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng l\'e0 xu\u7845 t t\u7915  \u272 \u7841 o gi\'e1o m\'e0 ra, nh\u432 ng ch\'fa tr\u7885 ng tu luy\u7879 n thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng h\u417 n, b\u7903 i v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \u7841 o s\u297  m\'e0 l\'e0 thu\u7853 t s\u297 . Ba gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c m\u7899 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \'edch \u273 \u7871 n. S\u432  m\'f4n c\u7911 a \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia b\u7855 t ngu\u7891 n t\u7915  \u272 \u7841 o ph\'e1i, b\u7889  c\u7909 c ki\u7871 n tr\'fac c\'f9ng v\u7899 i \u272 \u7841 o qu\'e1n c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 i\u7875 m gi\u7889 ng nhau, th\'f4n d\'e2n b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u g\u7885 i l\'e0 "\u272 \u7841 o qu\'e1n", nh\u432 ng phong c\'e1ch t\u7893 ng th\u7875  l\u7841 i thi\'ean v\u7873  ki\u7871 n tr\'fac Huy Ph\'e1i, ng\'f3i xanh t\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7855 ng, c\'f3 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7865 p m\u7897 c m\u7841 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7841 i m\'f4n b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'e9p h\u7901 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng g\'f5, ch\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e2n l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, anh \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y ch\u7901  em. Anh \u273 i v\'e0o b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n b\u7883  b\u7855 t th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\u7853 u l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7845 t an, ch\u7881  v\'e0o r\u7915 ng c\'e2y nh\u7887  c\'e1ch \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng xa n\'f3i: "Anh c\u7913  tr\u7889 n xa m\u7897 t ch\'fat s\u7869  t\u7889 t h\u417 n, \u7903  trong r\u7915 ng \'e2m, anh qua \u273 \'f3 ch\u7901  em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn c\u7853 u tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p c\u432 \u7901 i hai ti\u7871 ng, gi\u417  tay l\'f9i v\u7873  trong r\u7915 ng, c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1p: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, t\'f4i cam \u273 oan s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ph\'fat sau c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n t\u7915  xa \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n, m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng trung ni\'ean m\u7863 c \'e1o d\'e0i m\'e0u xanh \u273 \u7853 m m\u7903  c\u7917 a, sau khi h\u7855 n nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'ean m\u7863 t li\u7873 n to\'e1t ra v\u7867  kinh ng\u7841 c r\'f5 r\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'f3i: "Con l\'e0 do \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n l\'e3o ti\'ean sinh gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u \u273 \u7871 n, \'f4ng \u7845 y n\'f3i tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i con d\'ednh ph\u7843 i v\u7853 n \u273 en kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, t\u7899 i n\u417 i n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p lo\u7841 i tr\u7915 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i trung ni\'ean kia l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i l\u7897  v\u7867  gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh, li\'ean t\u7909 c g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "S\u432  th\'fac \u273 \'e3 nh\u7855 c qua v\u7899 i ch\'fang t\'f4i r\u7891 i, m\u7901 i ng\'e0i v\'e0o." V\u7915 a n\'f3i v\u7915 a m\u7901 i c\u7853 u \u273 i v\'e0o. \u272 \u7841 i m\'f4n \u7903  ph\'eda sau b\u7885 n h\u7885  im l\u7863 ng \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i, k\'edn k\u7869 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i trung ni\'ean n\'f3i Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u361 ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n tr\u7903  v\u7873 , ng\u432 \u7901 i trung ni\'ean d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat, d\u7851 n c\u7853 u t\u7899 i m\u7897 t *s\u7843 nh b\'ean ph\'eda sau, b\u432 ng tr\'e0 l\'ean m\u7901 i c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i, n\'f3i m\'ecnh \u273 i m\u7901 i s\u432  th\'fac v\'e0 s\u432  b\'e1 t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, n\'f3i xong li\u7873 n quay ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7901 i \u273 i, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i.\cb1 \

