\cb3 C\'f3 \uc0\u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p trong l\'fac v\'f4 t\'ecnh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y t\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n, n\'f3i "Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec, h\'f3a ra \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u t\'ean v\u7853 y sao? Th\u7853 t \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t nha!" . Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng g\u7841 t l\u432 \u417 ng t\'e2m m\'e0 \u273 \'e1p ph\u7843 i.\cb1 \
