\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u7903  n\'ean hung d\u7919 , g\u7845 p \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7897  \u273 \u7841 p m\u7897 t c\u432 \u7899 c l\'ean v\'e1n c\u7917 a, c\u7917 a g\u7895  nh\'ecn c\'f3 v\u7867  kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u7845 m th\'e9p kh\'f4ng ch\'fat s\u7913 t m\u7867 .\cb1 \
