\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n nh\u7919 ng k\u7867  \u273 \'f3 l\'e0m phi\u7873 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng gh\'e9t.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec v\uc0\u7853 y h\u7855 n ng\u7847 m \'e1m th\u7883  trong chuy\u7879 n phi\u7871 m h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y, \u7911 ng h\u7897  Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhanh ch\'f3ng t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, \u273 \u7875  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia to\'e0n b\u7897  ng\u7853 m mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ngo\'e0i d\u7921  li\u7879 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 sinh linh kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fat ki\'ean nh\u7851 n n\'e0o, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  sinh m\u7879 nh ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i b\'e9 nh\u7887  y\u7871 u \u7899 t c\u7911 a b\u7885 n ch\'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n im \u7855 ng tr\'e0o ph\'fang, t\u7921 a h\u7891  qu\'ean m\u7845 t m\'ecnh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng s\u7889 ng l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi y\'ean l\u7863 ng l\u7845 y ra di \u273 \u7897 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean mua cho h\u7855 n, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i tho\'e1ng bi\u7875 u l\u7897  n\'e9t m\u7863 t tr\'e2n qu\'fd. H\u7855 n g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n, b\u7843 o c\u7853 u \u273 i ra, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7863 ng l\u7869  \u273 \u7907 i h\u7891 i \'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ngh\'eanh Chi, em kh\'f4ng ra \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng k\u7867  \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 h\u7841  th\u7911  v\u7899 i A Di\'ean.\cb1 \
