\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 ang l\'fac n\'f4n n\'f3ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i tay m\'e1t l\u7841 nh \'f4m l\'ean eo m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\u7869  gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thanh \'e2m quen thu\u7897 c mang theo \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i vang l\'ean b\'ean tai: "Nh\u7899  t\'f4i r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh kh\'f4ng sao ch\uc0\u7913 ? L\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 qua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'ecnh ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e0m t\u7909 c, bao v\'e2y m\'ecnh ho\'e0n to\'e0n v\'f4 ngh\u297 a, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ch\u259 \u777 ng l\u7869  b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f2n bu\'f4n ng\u432 \u7901 i? Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7907 t hi\u7875 u ra, ch\u7881  s\u7907  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7843  s\u432  m\'f4n n\'e0y c\u7911 a \'f4ng sau khi bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 sinh l\'f2ng mu\u7889 n di\u7879 t tr\u7915  h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u v\u7889 n cho r\u7857 ng chuy\u7879 n m\'ecnh b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\u7845 n l\'ean l\'e0 m\u7897 t v\u7909  tranh c\'e3i d\'e2n s\u7921  "D\'e2n b\u7845 t t\u7889  quan b\u7845 t truy", s\u7869  ch\u7859 ng ai u\u7893 ng ph\'ed kh\'ed l\u7921 c quan t\'e2m; hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  m\u7899 i \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7881  s\u7907  \u7903  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o v\'e0 s\u432  m\'f4n c\u7911 a \'f4ng \u273 \'e3 coi vi\u7879 c n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 v\u7909  \'e1n h\'ecnh s\u7921 , \'e1c qu\u7927  h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7873 n t\u7897 i. L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3i v\u7899 i m\'ecnh nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\u7917 a th\u7853 t n\u7917 a gi\u7843  kia, ch\'ednh l\'e0 v\'ec d\u7909  d\u7895  m\'ecnh m\u7855 c c\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm m\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c g\'ec chui \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o l\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'f4n h\'f4n tr\'e1n c\u7853 u: "N\u7871 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng d\u7851 n t\'f4i ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0m sao s\u7869  d\u7877  d\'e0ng th\u7843  em?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7917 a v\u7851 n \u273 \'f3ng ch\u7863 t nh\u432  c\u361 , ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a r\u7891 i l\u7841 i truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n, tuy r\u7857 ng r\u7845 t nh\u7865  nh\u432 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe ra r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t t\u7847 ng v\'e1n c\u7917 a m\u7887 ng khi\u7871 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n b\'ean ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng ni\u7879 m ch\'fa tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p m\'e0 l\u7897 n x\u7897 n, c\'f2n c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 n l\'ean d\'e1n c\'e1c lo\u7841 i ph\'f9 ch\'fa l\'ean c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i \u273 \'e3 nghe r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n c\u7911 a \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n \u273 ang n\'f4n n\'f3ng n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3: "... S\u432  b\'e1, c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean kia c\'f2n \u7903  trong m\'e0! Uy l\u7921 c c\u7911 a b\'e1t ph\u432 \u417 ng tru t\'e0 tr\u7853 n th\u7847 n h\u7891 n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean kia th\'e2n th\u7875  l\u7841 i h\u432  nh\u432 \u7907 c, th\u7847 n h\u7891 n kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 m\u7841 nh, nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7881  s\u7907  s\u7869  tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p tr\u7903  n\'ean si ng\u7889 c, th\u7853 m ch\'ed b\u7887  m\u7841 ng!"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng \uc0\u7845 y \u273 ang n\'f3i m\'ecnh \u432  ? M\'ecnh s\u7869  ch\u7871 t?\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t \'e2m thanh gi\'e0 nua m\'e0 nghi\'eam kh\u7855 c vang l\'ean: "Quang Vi\u7877 n, ch\u7899  c\'f3 l\'f2ng d\u7841  \u273 \'e0n b\'e0! Ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  c\'f2n ch\u432 a m\'e3n tang k\u7923  m\'e0 con \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, h\'f4m nay kh\'f4ng nh\'e2n c\u417  h\u7897 i tr\u7915  b\u7887  n\'f3, ng\'e0y mai c\'f3 l\u7869  s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\u417  h\u7897 i n\u7919 a, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7863 c n\'f3 l\'e0m h\u7841 i th\u7871  gian. Minh S\u417 n, \u273 \u432 a s\u432  th\'fac Quang Vi\u7877 n c\u7911 a con \u273 i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i \u273 i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng ni\u7879 m ch\'fa \u273 \u7891 ng thanh ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng vang, l\'e0m cho \'f3c Tr\'ec Di\'ean ong ong, c\u7853 u v\'f4 l\u7921 c d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\u7917 a ng\u7891 i b\u7879 t xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'f5 r\'e0ng v\uc0\u7851 n \u273 ang l\'e0 ban ng\'e0y, trong ph\'f2ng l\u7841 i tr\u7903  n\'ean t\u7889 i \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u7845 t c\u7843  \'e1nh s\'e1ng \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  r\'fat \u273 i, c\'f9ng l\'fac \u273 \'f3 tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t hi\u7879 n ra nh\u7919 ng \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\'e2n m\'e0u \u273 o\u777  l\u7901  m\u7901  loang l\u7893 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7857 ng c\u7893  x\u432 a b\'ed hi\u7875 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd th\uc0\u7913 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u tr\u7903  n\'ean m\u417  h\u7891 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh, \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i \'f4m c\uc0\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mang theo tia l\u7841 nh th\u7845 u x\u432 \u417 ng, nh\u432 ng l\'e0 th\u7913  thanh minh duy nh\u7845 t trong \u273 \u7889 ng h\u7895 n t\u7841 p l\'fac n\'e0y. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \'f4m c\'e0ng ch\u7863 t h\u417 n, d\u7921 a tr\'ean vai h\u7855 n n\u7917 a kh\'e9p m\u7855 t nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng v\'f4 th\u7913 c th\'ec th\'e0o: "\u272 au \u273 \u7847 u..."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7909  h\'f4n l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o r\u417 i tr\'ean tr\'e1n c\u7853 u, nhu mi\u7871 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i luy\u7871 n ti\u7871 c r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd th\uc0\u7913 c trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c thanh t\u7881 nh, \u273 \u7847 u h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 au \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  m\u7855 t ra, m\u7855 t th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng kh\'ed \u273 en v\u7845 n v\'edt bao quanh to\'e0n th\'e2n m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng t\u7847 ng kh\'ed \u273 en sau khi ti\u7871 p x\'fac kh\'f4ng kh\'ed xung quanh l\u7841 i nh\u432  n\u432 \u7899 c g\u7863 p l\u7917 a, kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng b\u7883  thi\'eau \u273 \u7889 t b\u7889 c h\u417 i, m\'e0 theo \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i c\'f3 t\u7915 ng d\'f2ng kh\'ed \u273 en cu\u7891 n cu\u7897 n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c b\u7893  sung b\u7843 o v\u7879  c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t n\u417 i kh\'ed \u273 en xu\u7845 t ra nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. H\u7855 n \u273 ang thay m\'ecnh th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n x\'e2m h\u7841 i c\u7911 a tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p qu\u7927  d\u7883  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u?\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi..." C\u7853 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng k\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 a h\u7891  nh\'ecn ra c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n n\'f3i g\'ec, kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, du\u7895 i ng\'f3n tr\u7887  \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean m\'f4i c\u7853 u, ng\u259 n tr\u7903  l\u7901 i ch\u432 a ra kh\u7887 i mi\u7879 ng: "Ngoan, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng sao."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t m\'e0y h\u7855 n h\u417 i cong, t\u432  th\'e1i nh\'e0n h\u7841 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 t\u7915  ch\u7895  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n \u273 i ra r\u7891 i l\'ean xe ma, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng c\u432 \u7901 i th\u7871  n\'e0y nh\'ecn m\'ecnh, n\'f3i "Ai ng\u7901  em l\u7841 i ng\u7889 c \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c l\'ean nh\u7847 m xe" ; gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7895 i s\'e1ng s\u7899 m l\'fac ng\u7891 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh nh\'ecn m\'ecnh \u259 n \u273 i\u7875 m t\'e2m, c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i "Ng\'e0y mai mu\u7889 n \u259 n g\'ec?" ...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \'e1p t\u7899 i h\'f4n l\'ean m\'f4i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c d\'f9 \u273 \'e3 mu\u7889 n tin t\u432 \u7903 ng mu\u7889 n ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n, nh\u432 ng n\u7897 i t\'e2m v\u7851 n b\u7845 t an do d\u7921  v\u7851 n lo l\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng y\'ean, c\u7855 m r\u7877  s\'e2u trong l\'f2ng v\u7851 n l\'e0 n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i r\u7889 i tung qu\u7845 n l\u7851 n v\'e0o nhau, d\'f9 c\'f3 b\u7883  ch\'f4n v\'e0o trong \u273 \u7845 t, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ngh\u297 a l\'e0 m\u7847 m h\u7841 t \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng t\u7891 n t\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'ed \uc0\u273 en v\'e2y xung quanh b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng b\u7883  thi\'eau \u273 \u7889 t b\u7889 c h\u417 i, hoa v\u259 n c\u7911 a tr\u7853 n tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t ph\'e1t ra \'e1nh s\'e1ng m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng s\'e1ng, nh\u432 ng n\u417 i t\u7847 m m\u7855 t v\u7899 i t\u7899 i l\u7841 i l\'e0 kho\u7843 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 i \u273 en. Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7847 n m\'f2 th\'e2n th\u7875  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \'f4m ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y, d\u7921 a v\'e0o \'e1nh s\'e1ng \u273 \u7887  l\u7901  m\u7901  kia c\u7849 n th\u7853 n ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e9t tr\'ean g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t h\u7855 n, t\u7915 ng ch\'fat t\u7915 ng ch\'fat kh\u7855 c v\'e0o l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\u7915 a \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i n\u7909  h\'f4n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7915 a nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng l\u7863 p l\u7841 i t\'ean h\u7855 n "Ngh\'eanh Chi" "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi" ... C\'e1i t\'ean n\'e0y \u7903  trong l\'f2ng c\'e0ng c\u7855 m c\'e0ng s\'e2u, d\u7877  d\'e0ng \u273 em to\'e0n b\u7897  m\u7847 m h\u7841 t do d\u7921  b\u7845 t an n\u417 i \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng kia k\'e9o ra nghi\u7873 n n\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u sau hai ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7899 i t\'e1ch ra, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7921 a v\'e0o vai Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7903  d\u7889 c, c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  tho\'e1ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7897 c tho\u7841 i nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, v\'ec sao anh l\u7841 i qu\u7845 n l\'ean em..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng gi\uc0\u7889 ng o\'e1n tr\'e1ch, m\'e0 gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'fac l\'e0m n\u361 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau h\u7887 i "Anh r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c th\'edch em \u7903  \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0o" . Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u da m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7887 ng, c\'e1ch n\'f3i sau c\u7853 u h\u7887 i kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7853 t l\'e2u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i t\u7915  b\u7887  hi v\u7885 ng nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1p \'e1n, h\u7855 n m\u7899 i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "... Khi c\'f2n s\u7889 ng t\'f4i lu\'f4n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh \u273 ang t\'ecm ki\u7871 m th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh mu\u7889 n t\'ecm c\'e1i g\'ec. L\'fac \u7845 y th\'e2n th\u7875  t\'f4i r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 n\'ean ch\u7871 t s\u7899 m, nh\u432 ng t\'f4i kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n d\'f9ng h\u7871 t th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n c\u7889  g\u7855 ng k\'e9o d\'e0i h\u417 i t\'e0n m\'e0 s\u7889 ng, ch\'ednh l\'e0 ngh\u297  s\u7889 ng th\'eam m\u7897 t ng\'e0y... bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u s\u7869  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 "... Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng t\'f4i v\u7851 n ch\u7871 t. Nh\u432 ng em \u273 \'e3 xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n. T\'f4i li\u7873 n bi\u7871 t, \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean tay \u273 \'e8 l\'ean ng\u7921 c tr\'e1i n\u417 i tr\'e1i tim, ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\'fat s\u7921  s\u7889 ng v\'e0 nh\u7883 p \u273 \u7853 p n\'e0o, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i r\u7845 t \u273 \u7847 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\uc0\u7915  \u273 \'f3 v\u7873  sau t\'f4i li\u7873 n ngh\u297 , \u273 em em nh\u7889 t \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh t\'f4i, kh\'f4ng cho em r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i t\'f4i n\u7919 a." Ch\u7845 p ni\u7879 m n\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t l\u7841 i c\u7913  v\u7853 y m\'e0 th\'e0nh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\u7903 i ngu\u7891 n t\u7915  khao kh\'e1t b\u7843 n n\u259 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  v\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c nhau, ch\'fang ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng t\u7915  th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7845 p ni\u7879 m c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t kh\'e1t c\u7847 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "A Di\'ean, \uc0\u273 \u7915 ng r\u7901 i b\u7887  t\'f4i." H\u7855 n c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n l\'ean t\'f3c mai tr\'ean th\'e1i d\u432 \u417 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng "\u431 m..." m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng. D\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  b\u7843 o v\u7879  c\u7911 a kh\'ed \u273 en, \'fd th\u7913 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  duy tr\'ec thanh t\u7881 nh, nh\u432 ng bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  v\'e0 m\u7879 t m\u7887 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng d\'e2ng l\'ean. C\u7853 u v\'f4 th\u7913 c \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "V\u7853 y anh \'f4m em \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u432 a tay k\'e9o c\u7853 u \'e1p v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c: "\u272 \u7913 a ng\u244 \u769 c, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \'f4m em sao."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  v\u7895  v\u7873  l\u432 ng c\u7853 u, nh\'ecn c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng ch\'fat ch\'ecm s\'e2u v\'e0o m\u7897 ng \u273 \u7865 p \u273 en ng\u7885 t, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c y\'ean l\u7863 ng kh\'f4ng g\u7907 n s\'f3ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'ed \uc0\u273 en v\'e2y xung quanh b\u7885 n h\u7885  ng\'e0y c\'e0ng d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n lan kh\u7855 p, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ng\u432 ng t\u7909  l\u7841 i ph\u7911  l\u7845 p to\'e0n b\u7897  kh\'f4ng gian.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m l\u7917 a v\u432 \u7907 ng n\u432 \u7899 c thi\u7871 u, ch\'fat n\u432 \u7899 c d\'f4\u803 i l\'ean s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7889 c h\u417 i; nh\u432 ng trong bi\u7875 n l\u7899 n m\'eanh m\'f4ng, l\u7917 a n\'e0o c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\'e1y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i \'f4n nhu nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng s\u7901  m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Ngoan, ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c cho t\u7889 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t h\u7855 n ch\u432 a ho\'e0n to\'e0n r\'fat \u273 i, cong kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng, hai tay \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, quay ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \'e1 v\u259 ng c\u7917 a tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1nh c\uc0\u7917 a m\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7903  ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t h\u7855 n l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  gi\u7845 y, kh\'ed \u273 en cu\u7897 n tr\'e0o m\'e3nh li\u7879 t sau l\u432 ng h\u7855 n cu\u7891 n cu\u7897 n tr\'e0n ra t\u7915  c\'e1nh c\u7917 a m\u7903  l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i th\u7873 m \u273 \'e1, l\'e0 t\u7915 ng g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t s\u7907  h\'e3i m\u7897 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i th\'ec \u273 ang \u7903  trong b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang an v\u7883  b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u432 a \u273 \u7907 i c\u7853 u m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'f3i: "Tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac \u273 i v\'e0o trong t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 \u7849 n danh t\u7889  c\'e1o tr\'ean n\'fai c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7893  ch\u7913 c truy\u7873 n b\'e1 t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng t\'e0 gi\'e1o phi ph\'e1p, c\'f2n c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7891  th\u7915 a d\u7883 p m\'f9a thu tr\u7901 i hanh v\u7853 t kh\'f4 ph\'f3ng h\u7887 a \u273 \u7889 t n\'fai. Sau \u273 \'f3 b\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ki\u7875 m tra, em ng\u7911  thi\u7871 p \u273 i, t\'f4i li\u7873 n \u273 \u7863 t em l\'ean t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 ven \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7885 n h\u7885  t\u432 \u7903 ng em h\'f4n m\'ea s\u7869  \u273 \u432 a em \u273 i vi\u7879 n." D\'f9 sao \u273 \'e1m thu\u7853 t s\u297  \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \u7841 o s\u297  ch\'ednh ph\'e1i, h\u7855 n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh t\u7889  c\'e1o r\u7845 t l\'e0 \u273 \'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi bi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u h\u7887 i l\'e0 ai, c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "B\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng giam \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f4i, sau khi \u273 i ra th\'ec t\'f4i nh\u7889 t bo\u803 n h\u7885  v\'e0o trong gian ph\'f2ng \u273 \'f3, d\'f9 sao tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p b\'ean trong c\u361 ng do ch\'ednh h\u7885  b\u7889  tr\'ed, \u273 \u7875  b\u7885 n h\u7885  gieo gi\'f3 g\u7863 t b\'e3o. N\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7843 nh s\'e1t \u273 \u7871 n \u273 i\u7873 u tra \u273 \'e3 th\u7843  b\u7885 n h\u7885  ra r\u7891 i." T\u7845 t nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7843  d\u7877  d\'e0ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac h\uc0\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i \'e1nh m\u7855 t h\u417 i cong l\'ean, s\'e2u kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e1y: "A Di\'ean, kh\'f4ng n\'ean v\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan m\'e0 hao t\u7893 n t\'e2m s\u7913 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi," Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng g\u7885 i h\u7855 n, "B\'e2y gi\u7901  th\u7853 t s\u7921  ngay c\u7843  ch\u7871 t em c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng s\u7907  r\u7891 i... Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7843  cho anh."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi y\'ean l\u7863 ng n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t tay c\u7853 u: "V\u7853 y c\u7913  \u7903  chung m\u7897 t ch\u7895  v\u7899 i t\'f4i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 ang mu\u7889 n n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3, l\'fac n\'e0y y t\'e1 \u273 i v\'e0o, kh\'f3 hi\u7875 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Gi\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7889  b\u7843 y, c\u7853 u \u273 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i ai v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fang t\'fang li\uc0\u7871 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, ho khan m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai c\u7843 , t\'f4i \u273 ang h\u7885 c c\'f4ng th\u7913 c n\u7845 u \u259 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi li\u7871 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "G\u7841 t qu\u7927  g\'ec \u273 \'f3, ch\u432 a th\u7845 y em l\'e0m c\u417 m bao gi\u7901  \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i b\uc0\u7853 y, r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'fac c\'f2n th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng b\'e0i v\u7883  anh trong nh\'e0 m\u7895 i ng\'e0y em \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0m c\u417 m d\'e2ng cho anh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e9n l\'fat o\'e1n th\u7847 m, nh\u432 ng v\u432 \u7899 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u7903  \u273 \'e2y n\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o ph\u7843 n b\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Y t\'e1 mi\uc0\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n l\u7901 i gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'e0y, nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 o nh\u7883 p tim v\'e0 huy\u7871 t \'e1p cho c\u7853 u, th\'f4ng b\'e1o t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, l\u7841 i k\u7875  cho c\u7853 u nghe chuy\u7879 n c\u7853 u h\'f4n m\'ea d\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n n\'fai \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u432 a \u273 i vi\u7879 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Y t\'e1 n\'f3i: "C\uc0\u7853 u an t\'e2m t\u297 nh d\u432 \u7905 ng \u273 i, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 v\'ec kh\'f4ng ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i t\u7889 t th\'f4i. \u272 \'e3 b\'e1o cho b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u r\u7891 i, r\u7845 t nhanh h\u7855 n s\u7869  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 ang nghi ho\u7863 c l\'e0 b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u n\'e0o, T\u7915  Giang \u273 \'e3 m\u7897 t th\'e2n gi\'f3 b\u7909 i m\u7879 t m\u7887 i ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 c\'f9ng c\uc0\u7843 m \u273 \u7897 ng l\u7841 i th\u7845 y r\u7845 t \'e1y n\'e1y, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i l\'e0m phi\u7873 n T\u7915  Giang ph\u7843 i ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i coi \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ch\u7859 ng h\u7873  \u273 \u7875  \'fd, khi \u7845 y v\u7915 a \u273 \'fang l\'fac h\u7855 n g\u7885 i cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean, sau khi nh\'e2n vi\'ean ch\u259 m s\'f3c \u273 ang chu\u7849 n b\u7883  li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 nh\u7853 n \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i th\'f4ng b\'e1o t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng, h\u7855 n li\u7873 n nhanh ch\'f3ng t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y. H\u7855 n bi\u7871 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\u7885  h\'e0ng g\'ec \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, b\u7841 n b\'e8 qua l\u7841 i th\'e2n thi\u7871 t nh\u7845 t \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 m\'ecnh. H\u7855 n h\u7887 i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh c\u417  b\u7843 n, bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec chuy\u7879 n g\'ec l\u7899 n c\u361 ng y\'ean t\'e2m, trao \u273 \u7893 i v\u7899 i b\'e1c s\u297  t\u7889 i h\'f4m nay n\u7857 m vi\u7879 n quan s\'e1t m\u7897 t ng\'e0y, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec th\'ec ng\'e0y mai xu\u7845 t vi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n chuy\u7875 n gh\u7871  ng\u7891 i \u7903  b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u417 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, v\u7915 a ch\u417 i v\u7915 a t\'e1n d\'f3c v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 ? Ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7853 u \u273 \'e2u? Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\'f9a xu\'e2n n\u259 m nay c\u7853 u y\'eau \u273 \u432 \u417 ng \'e0, b\u7885 n t\u7899  h\u7865 n c\u7853 u \u273 i t\u7909  h\u7885 p c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7865 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Th\u7871  n\'e0o l\u7841 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u273 i leo n\'fai ch\u417 i, \u7903  vi\u7879 n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng th\u7845 y g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7887 i han g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i \u7903  b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng kh\u7869  h\'f4n m\'ed m\u7855 t m\'ecnh v\'e9n t\'f3c m\'ecnh, \'fap \'fap m\u7903  m\u7903  n\'f3i: "H\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
