\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\uc0\u297  m\'ecnh v\'e0 T\u7915  Giang l\'e0 b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o l\u7915 a g\u7841 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u hi\u7875 u g\u7889 c r\u7877  lu\'f4n li\u7873 n nhau, c\'e2u n\'f3i d\u7889 i T\u7915  Giang n\'e0y kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ho\'e0n ch\u7881 nh, s\u7899 m mu\u7897 n c\u361 ng s\u7869  b\u7841 i l\u7897 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e3 ch\u7871 t? ! T\u7915  Giang l\u7853 p t\u7913 c bu\'f4ng di d\u7897 ng tr\u7915 ng to m\u7855 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda v\u7883  h\u7843 o h\u7919 u \u273 ang ng\u7891 i d\u7921 a v\'e0o \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7859 ng l\u7869  v\'ec chia tay t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng qu\'e1 s\'e2u n\'ean m\u7899 i n\'f3i v\u7853 y? Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean nguy\u7873 n r\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i ta nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7913 ? H\u7855 n bi\u7871 t Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i cay nghi\u7879 t \'e1c \u273 \u7897 c nh\u432  th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bu\'f4ng m\uc0\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng, l\u7863 ng l\u7869  n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "\u7914 , \u273 \'e3 qua \u273 \u7901 i r\u7891 i, v\'e0o m\'f9a h\'e8. L\'e0 t\u7899  v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n s\u7921  th\u7853 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t ti\u7871 n s\u297  x\'e3 h\u7897 i h\u7885 c, nh\u432 ng nh\u7919 ng t\'e1c ph\u7849 m T\u7915  Giang y\'eau th\'edch m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m th\u7921 c t\u7871  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3. L\'fac kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec l\'e0m h\u7855 n th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'edch xem t\'e1c ph\u7849 m ngh\u7879  thu\u7853 t c\'f3 phong v\u7883 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  hoa c\'e1t c\'e1nh t\u7887 a h\u432 \u417 ng, mang theo n\u7895 i bu\u7891 n v\'f4 c\u7899  kh\'f4ng ho\'e0n m\u7929 , d\'f9ng n\'f3 \u273 \u7875  b\u7891 i d\u432 \u7905 ng, an \u7911 i, g\u7897 t r\u7917 a t\'e2m h\u7891 n l\u259 n l\u7897 n trong th\u7871  t\u7909 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o m\u7845 y l\u7901 i mi\'eau t\u7843  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c v\'e0 l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, theo n\'e3o b\u7893  c\u7911 a T\u7915  Giang, ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m ngh\u7873  t\u7921  do, l\u7919  h\'e0nh mu\'f4n n\u417 i, ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, l\'fac r\u7843 nh r\u7895 i s\u7869  g\u7917 i b\'e0i cho s\'e1ch b\'e1o trang web du l\u7883 ch, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 b\'e0i vi\u7871 t. Cho \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\u7885 , trong b\'f3ng \u273 \'eam \u7903  Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  ph\u7891 n hoa m\'e0 m\u297  lo\u7841 n, h\u7855 n v\'f4 t\'ecnh li\u7871 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'eam m\u7897 t l\u7847 n. V\'ec v\u7853 y t\u7921 a nh\u432  hoa b\u7891  c\'f4ng anh cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u361 ng s\u7869  r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921  theo c\u7853 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883 , h\u7871 t l\'f2ng ch\u259 m s\'f3c cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng ng\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, t\u7915  \u273 \'f3 tr\u7843 i qua m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n th\u7901 i gian ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o v\'f4 \u432 u v\'f4 lo.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 s\u7903  th\'edch chung quy kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o d\u7913 t b\u7887 , \u273 \u7871 n m\'f9a h\'e8 h\u7855 n l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a m\u7897 t m\'ecnh b\u432 \u7899 c l\'ean con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7919  h\'e0nh, tr\u432 \u7899 c khi \u273 i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u: "Em \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\u7901  t\'f4i, l\u7847 n n\'e0y t\'f4i s\u7869  tr\u7903  v\u7873  r\u7845 t nhanh th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng l\'e0m vi\u7879 c sinh ho\u7841 t h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y, \u273 \u7907 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau tr\u7903  v\u7873 , m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\u7885  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i t\u7915  d\'e3y s\u7889  quen thu\u7897 c, kinh h\u7881  \u7845 n nghe m\'e1y, nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i l\'e0 tin \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  n\u7919 a...\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kia gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u417 n gi\'f3, im \u7855 ng v\'f4 h\'ecnh th\u7893 i qua l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\'fac h\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n xu\'e2n v\u7873  hoa n\u7903 , l\'fac h\u7855 n \u273 i ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i v\u7841 n v\u7853 t hoang vu.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p b\u7883  n\'e3o b\u7893  c\u7911 a ch\'ednh m\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7907 c kh\'f3c, th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n ng\u432 \u7907 c t\'e2m ch\u7881  th\u7845 y trong phim \u7843 nh ti\u7875 u thuy\u7871 t l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  x\u7843 y \u273 \u7871 n v\u7899 i v\u7883  h\u7843 o h\u7919 u nh\'ecn qua v\'f4 c\'f9ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. H\u7855 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m h\u7887 i th\'eam c\'e2u n\'e0o n\u7919 a, t\u7921  gi\'e1c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\'f3i th\'eam m\u7897 t c\'e2u l\'e0 \u273 \'e2m l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7897 t \u273 ao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7915 a c\u417  t\u7887  r\'f5 l\u7853 p tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh: "Tuy r\u7857 ng h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng t\u7899  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c h\u7855 n \u273 ang s\u7889 ng b\'ean t\u7899 . T\u7899  ngh\u297  t\u7899  s\u7869  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c tr\'f4ng coi h\u7855 n, c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  Giang li\'ean t\u7909 c g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , t\u7899  hi\u7875 u m\'e0. Kh\'f4ng sao h\u7871 t, t\u7899  hi\u7875 u, t\u7899  \u7911 ng h\u7897  c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng r\u7845 t nghi ho\u7863 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\u7841 i c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  \u7911 ng h\u7897  c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n l\'e2u n\u259 m th\u7871  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n th\uc0\u7875  c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau li\u7873 n l\'e1i xe c\'f9ng T\u7915  Giang tr\u7903  v\u7873  T\'f4 D\'e2n th\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac tr\'ean xe Tr\'ec Di\'ean y\'ean l\uc0\u7863 ng nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i \u7903  gh\u7871  ph\u7909 , n\'f3i v\u7899 i T\u7915  Giang \u273 ang mu\u7889 n m\u7903  c\u7917 a xe ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c: "L\'e3o T\u7915  c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i ph\'eda sau \u273 i... \u7914 m, ph\'eda sau an to\'e0n h\u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi v\uc0\u7873  nh\'e0 hai tu\u7847 n, l\'fac \u7903  \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t b\u432 u ki\u7879 n, ng\u432 \u7901 i g\u7917 i l\'e0 \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y \'f4ng b\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7889  g\u7855 ng b\u7843 o v\u7879  Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\'e0 b\u7883  s\u432  b\'e1 k\'eau \u273 \u7879  t\u7917  d\u7851 n \u273 i, kh\'f4ng tham gia chuy\u7879 n ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7903  hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i b\u7903 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ki\u7871 p. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi sau khi \u273 i ra l\u7853 t ng\u432 \u7907 c th\u7871  c\u7901  li\u7873 n nh\u7889 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  \u273 \'f3 v\'e0o gian ph\'f2ng v\u7869  b\'e1t ph\u432 \u417 ng tru t\'e0 tr\u7853 n kia, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\u7889  \'fd tr\u7843  th\'f9 \'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n lu\'f4n \u273 em vi\u7879 c b\u7843 o to\'e0n b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7863 t \u7903  v\u7883  tr\'ed th\u7913  nh\u7845 t. L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\'ecm ra \'f4ng \u273 ang t\u7841 m th\u7901 i \u7903  trong c\u259 n bi\u7879 t th\u7921  kia thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a \u273 \'e3 h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t \'f4ng, sau \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\u7843 i quay v\u7873  t\'ecm Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, m\u7863 c d\'f9 \'f4ng bi\u7871 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  g\u7863 p b\u7845 t tr\u7855 c, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t n\u259 ng l\u7921 c m\'ecnh c\'f3 h\u7841 n kh\'f4ng l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec, n\u7871 u th\u7915 a d\u7883 p *ngh\u297 a d\u361 ng th\'ec c\'f9ng l\u7855 m ch\u7881  g\'f3p th\'eam \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t c\'e1i m\u7841 ng gi\'e0, \'f4ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ng\u259 n c\u7843 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7921  t\'ecm \u273 \u7871 n l\u432 \u7899 i qu\u7927 .\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (ngh\uc0\u297 a d\u361 ng: anh d\u361 ng \u273 \u7845 u tranh v\'ec ch\'ednh ngh\u297 a)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m nay c\uc0\u361 ng v\u7853 y, b\'e1t ph\u432 \u417 ng tru t\'e0 tr\u7853 n truy\u7873 n th\u7915 a t\u7915  th\u7901 i Minh tri\u7873 u c\u7911 a s\u432  m\'f4n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng tr\u7845 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1c qu\u7927  kia, tr\'e1i l\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i trong s\u432  m\'f4n \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  ph\u7843 n ph\u7879 . L\'e3o s\u432  b\'e1 \u273 \'e3 g\u7847 n tr\u259 m tu\u7893 i l\u7841 i c\'e0ng b\u7903 i tu\u7893 i gi\'e0 m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c uy \'e1p c\u7911 a tru t\'e0 tr\u7853 n, sau khi \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7913 u ra ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n b\u7843 y ng\'e0y \u273 \'e3 bu\'f4ng tay nh\'e2n th\u7871 , tr\u432 \u7899 c khi \u273 i v\u7851 n c\'f2n l\u7863 p \u273 i l\u7863 p l\u7841 i khuy\'ean r\u259 n \u273 \u7879  t\u7917  ch\u7899  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 \u7909 ng \u273 \u7871 n \'e1c qu\u7927  kia. \'d4ng \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n v\'f4 \'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u259 m \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng gi\'fap \'f4ng, sau \u273 \'f3 \'f4ng gi\'fap Tr\'ec Di\'ean lo\u7841 i tr\u7915  qu\u7927  kh\'ed m\'ea t\'e2m, v\u7889 n l\'e0 k\u7871 t xu\u7889 ng thi\u7879 n duy\'ean, th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\u7841 i k\u7871 t th\'f9.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong b\uc0\u432 u ki\u7879 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t l\'e1 th\u432  v\'e0 m\u7897 t b\'ecnh ng\u7885 c nh\u7887 . Trong th\u432  \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng Quang Vi\u7877 n b\'e0y t\u7887  h\u7893  th\u7865 n v\'e0 day d\u7913 t \u273 \'e3 l\u7915 a g\u7841 t d\u7909  c\u7853 u \u273 i s\u432  m\'f4n, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i h\u7841 i c\u7853 u r\u417 i v\'e0o hi\u7875 m c\u7843 nh, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n *h\u7889 i kh\'ed x\'fai qu\u7849 y tuy\u7879 t kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\u7915 a g\u7841 t c\u7853 u, trong b\'ecnh ng\u7885 c l\'e0 t\'e1m m\u432 \u417 i m\u7889 t vi\'ean \u273 an tr\u7915  h\u7889 i, m\u7895 i n\u259 m \u259 n m\u7897 t vi\'ean lo\u7841 i b\u7887  t\'e0 h\u7889 i m\u7897 t n\u259 m nay l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (h\uc0\u7889 i: xui x\u7867 o, v\u7853 n \u273 en)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tan l\'e0m Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7847 m b\'ecnh ng\u7885 c tr\u7903  v\u7873  t\'ecm Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn nh\'ecn, n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\u7885 a, c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, \u259 n \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 y gi\u7901  Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i y\'ean t\'e2m \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi \uc0\u259 n c\u417 m t\u7889 i xong Tr\'ec Di\'ean xem tivi, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh \'f4m laptop kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 ang l\'e0m g\'ec, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7851 n nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7897 t nhi\'ean Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7875  laptop l\'ean b\'e0n, nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i qua \'f4m l\u7845 y eo c\u7853 u, vu\u7889 t ve h\'f4n c\u7893  c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  th\'e2n m\u7853 t b\u7845 t th\'ecnh l\'ecnh t\u7853 p k\'edch l\'e0m tay ch\'e2n lu\u7889 ng cu\u7889 ng, m\u7863 t sung huy\u7871 t \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng, hai tay \'f4m l\'ean c\u7893  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, l\u7855 p b\u7855 p h\u7887 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, l\'fac c\'f2n s\u7889 ng anh c\u361 ng th\u7871  n\'e0y \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o l\'f2ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\'f4n: "\u272 o\'e1n m\'f2 c\'e1i g\'ec, ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i b\u7883  b\u7879 nh tim nghi\'eam tr\u7885 ng, b\'e1c s\u297  kh\'f4ng cho t\'f4i v\u7853 n \u273 \u7897 ng k\u7883 ch li\u7879 t..."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \'e1p \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean tai Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "... L\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o c\'f3 phong l\u432 u kho\'e1i ho\u7841 t nh\u432  khi th\'e0nh qu\u7927 ..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7889 c t\u7841 i ch\u7895 , m\u7863 t c\'e0ng \u273 \u7887  h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\
