\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t nhanh l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i n\u259 m, ch\u432 a \u273 \u7907 i qua Nguy\'ean \u272 \'e1n, \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh \u273 \'e3 g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i k\'eau Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7919  kh\'ed h\u7855 n r\u7845 t g\u7845 p, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i t\u7899 i c\'f9ng, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng xin ngh\u7881  l\'e1i xe \u273 \u7871 n Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883 . V\u7915 a m\u7899 i v\'e0o c\u7917 a \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, trong nh\'e0 v\u7855 ng ng\u7855 t l\u7841 nh tanh, h\'ecnh nh\u432  ch\u7911  nh\'e0 \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\'e2u kh\'f4ng quay v\u7873  \u7903 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n, sau khi c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh m\u7899 i m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n ch\'f9m ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7899 i nh\'ecn r\'f5 ch\'fa v\u7853 y m\'e0 ch\u7889 ng m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c g\u7853 y batoong, ch\'e2n tr\'e1i ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7921 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  trong m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam gi\'e0 \u273 i hai m\u432 \u417 i tu\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh d\u7851 n c\u7853 u t\u7899 i s\'f4 pha ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, r\u7845 t b\'ecnh t\u297 nh m\'e0 n\'f3i lu\'f4n v\'e0o \u273 i\u7875 m ch\'ednh: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, c\'f4ng ty c\u7911 a ch\'fa s\u7855 p kh\'f4ng xong, n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 l\'fac th\'e0nh l\u7853 p cha m\u7865  con c\u361 ng c\'f3 \u273 \u7847 u t\u432 , b\'e2y gi\u7901  trong tay con c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau c\u7893  ph\u7847 n c\'f4ng ty, ch\'fa c\'f2n ch\'fat t\'e0i s\u7843 n, c\'f3 th\u7875  d\'f9ng gi\'e1 g\u7845 p 1.5 l\u7847 n gi\'e1 th\u7883  tr\u432 \u7901 ng hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  mua."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 p b\u7855 p kinh h\'e3i, nh\'ecn tr\'e1i nh\'ecn ph\u7843 i, h\u7887 i: "L\'e0m sao th\u7871  \u7841 ? M\u7907  v\u7899 i \u272 \'ecnh \u272 \'ecnh \u273 \'e2u ch\'fa?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u: "Ch\'fa v\'e0 c\'f4 ta \u273 \'e3 ly h\'f4n r\u7891 i. \u272 \'ecnh \u272 \'ecnh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i con g\'e1i ch\'fa."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u v\'ec c\'f4ng ty v\'e0 s\u7921  nghi\u7879 p m\'e0 ph\u7845 n \u273 \u7845 u, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac cu\u7889 i l\u7841 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n, b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'f4ng ty c\u361 ng s\u7909 p \u273 \u7893  r\u7891 i, v\u7853 y m\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 a ch\'e1u trai b\'ean ngo\u7841 i n\'e0y. V\'ec v\u7853 y h\u7855 n d\u7889 c h\u7871 t kh\u7843  n\u259 ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng mu\u7889 n b\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng b\u7883  t\u7893 n th\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i. L\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875 ... Trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u ch\'fa lu\'f4n l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7845 t t\'e0i gi\u7887 i r\u7845 t n\u7895  l\u7921 c c\u361 ng r\u7845 t hi\u7871 u th\u7855 ng, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng sao l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u432  v\u7853 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Ch\u7891 ng c\'f4 ta b\'e2y gi\u7901  L\u432 u Th\u7883 nh H\u7843 i, ch\'ednh l\'e0 \'f4ng ch\u7911  c\u7911 a Th\u7883 nh H\u7843 i, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  l\'e2u r\u7891 i, l\'e0 ch\'fa qu\'e1 b\u7853 n r\u7897 n, v\u7853 y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra. Ch\'fa c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng c\'f4 ta, chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a c\'f4ng ty c\'f4 ta c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7873 u n\'f3i h\u7871 t cho L\u432 u Th\u7883 nh H\u7843 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng Th\u7883 nh H\u7843 i n\'e0y, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\'e0 quan h\u7879  c\u7841 nh tranh v\u7899 i ch\'fa, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 quy m\'f4 danh ti\u7871 ng m\u7895 i ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng c\'f4ng ty ch\'fa n\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\u7883  \'e1p ch\u7871 , ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\u7887 i: "Ch\'e2n c\u7911 a ch\'fa... ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh n\'f3i: "L\'fac ch\'fa \u273 ang xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u th\'ec bi\u7871 t tin \u273 \'f3, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i l\u7841 i b\u7883  cao huy\u7871 t \'e1p, ch\'f3ng m\u7863 t n\'ean ng\'e3. C\u361 ng may ch\u7881  c\'f2n hai b\u7853 c thang, h\u417 n n\u7919 a \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng b\u7883  \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 \'f9i b\u7883  t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n l\u7899 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  tr\u7883  kh\u7887 i kh\'f4ng \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\uc0\u7883  kh\u7887 i hay kh\'f4ng c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng nhau." \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh c\u432 \u7901 i kho\'e1t tay, trong n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f3 gi\u7845 u kh\u7893  \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 n nh\'e0 r\u7897 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y b\u7895 ng ch\u7889 c l\u7897  v\u7867  tr\u7889 ng tr\u7843 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\'e1ng sa s\'fat th\u7871  n\'e0y c\u7911 a ch\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  b\u7843 n th\'e2n khi c\'f2n b\'e9, ch\'fa tuy r\u7857 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec b\u7853 n r\u7897 n n\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng v\'ec ch\'fa d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed sung t\'fac, l\'fac n\'e0o c\u361 ng tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n ch\'fa \u273 \u7871 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u th\'edch b\'e1m theo qu\u7845 n quanh ch\'fa. C\u7853 u qu\u7843  th\u7921 c kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o \u273 em ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fa tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng khi \u273 \'f3 li\'ean h\u7879  v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng sa s\'fat tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u lo l\u7855 ng b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y c\u7911 a \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh, \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n \u7903  l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\u7853 u n\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'ecn l\'ean tr\u7847 n nh\'e0 m\'e0u \u273 en \u273 \u7871 n xu\u7845 t th\u7847 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7901  s\u7901  v\'e0nh tai c\u7853 u: "Sao c\'f2n ch\u432 a ng\u7911 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em \uc0\u273 ang suy ngh\u297 , c\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u273 \'fang nh\u432  l\u7901 i \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e3o gia n\'f3i hay kh\'f4ng, l\'e0 em li\'ean lu\u7925  ch\'fa." Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7903  to m\u7855 t nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng th\'edch n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7921 a theo l\u7901 i l\'e3o b\u7883 p b\u7907 m kia, A Di\'ean mang x\'fai qu\u7849 y \u273 \u7871 n cho ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh l\'e0 v\'ec t\'e0 kh\'ed nh\u7853 p th\u7875 , t\'e0 kh\'ed nh\u7853 p th\u7875  l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7853 u v\'e0 h\u7855 n h\'f2a h\u7907 p... N\'e0o c\'f3 \u273 \u7841 o l\'fd nh\u432  v\u7853 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7915 ng n\'f3i m\'f2," h\u7855 n n\'f3i, "M\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i d\u7921 a v\'e0o ch\'ednh m\'ecnh, \u273 \u7915 ng tin m\u7845 y th\u7913  phong ki\u7871 n m\'ea t\'edn n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t con qu\u7927  d\u7841 y c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'ean tin phong ki\u7871 n m\'ea t\'edn. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i ki\u7875 u g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 ch\'fa v\u7851 n lu\'f4n r\u7845 t n\u7895  l\u7921 c, c\u361 ng r\u7845 t c\'f3 t\'e0i... Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7855 n n\u7895  l\u7921 c c\'f3 t\'e0i n\u259 ng, cho n\'ean kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ngay t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u c\'f4ng ty h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng r\u7845 t t\u7889 t \u432 ? B\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 do ch\'ednh h\u7855 n \u273 \'e1nh m\u7845 t \'fd ch\'ed chi\u7871 n \u273 \u7845 u, ph\u432 \u417 ng ph\'e1p c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng l\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e1n c\u7901 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u7903  m\'ecnh, m\u7903  to hai m\u7855 t nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng n\'f3i l\u7901 i n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4n l\'ean m\u7855 t c\u7853 u: "Sao l\u7841 i nh\'ecn t\'f4i nh\u432  v\u7853 y? Kh\'f4ng tin \u432 ? V\u7853 y em c\'f3 tin trong m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n h\u7855 n thay \u273 \u7893 i th\u7871  c\u7909 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "N\uc0\u259 m \u273 \'f3 b\u7885 n h\u7885  g\u7885 i t\'f4i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , em n\'f3i xem l\'e0 t\'f4i m\u7897 t th\'e2n b\u7879 nh t\u7853 t m\u432 \u7907 n v\u7883  th\u7871  Di\u7879 p gia, hay l\'e0 Di\u7879 p gia m\u432 \u7907 n v\u7883  th\u7871  t\'f4i?" H\u7855 n th\'e2n m\u7853 t \'f4m l\u7845 y vai Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng th\'e8m \u273 \u7875  \'fd l\u7901 i n\'f3i v\'e0 h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau gi\u7889 ng m\u7897 t con kh\u7893 ng t\u432 \u7899 c x\'f2e \u273 u\'f4i t\'ecm b\u7841 n \u273 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7853 y s\u7899 m m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u273 \u7913 ng trong b\u7871 p nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9ng nguy\'ean li\u7879 u n\u7845 u \u259 n c\'f2n s\'f3t l\u7841 i trong nh\'e0 l\'e0m ra m\u7897 t b\u7919 a s\'e1ng th\u7883 nh so\u7841 n, sau \u273 \'f3 gi\'fap b\u432 ng l\'ean b\'e0n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh sau khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y r\u7845 t kinh ng\u7841 c, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Con l\'e0m \u432 ? !"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a g\u7841 t l\u432 \u417 ng t\'e2m g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e1p: "Con l\'e0m \u7841 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh r\u7845 t c\u7843 m kh\'e1i: "Ch\'fa nh\u7899  l\'fac con c\'f2n h\u7885 c \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881  v\u7873  nh\'e0 chi\'ean tr\u7913 ng cho b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  chi\'ean ch\'e1y n\u7891 i, m\u7845 y n\u259 m qua s\u7889 ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh b\'ean ngo\'e0i, qu\u7843  nhi\'ean ti\u7871 n b\u7897  kh\'f4ng \'edt."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe xong li\u7873 n gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "H\'f3a ra l\'e0 th\u7871  sao, v\u7853 y t\'f4i tha th\u7913  cho em l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean t\'f4i v\'e0o c\u7917 a em \u273 \'e3 n\u7845 u m\'ec g\'f3i cho t\'f4i \u259 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat h\u7855 n l\u7841 i b\u7893  sung: "A Di\'ean, k\u7923  th\u7853 t t\'f4i r\u7845 t th\'edch \u259 n c\u417 m em l\'e0m. \u7914 m, \u273 \u7891  em l\'e0m cho t\'f4i, so v\u7899 i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n ngo\'e0i ngon h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng c\u259 m ph\u7851 n, c\u7853 u th\u7853 t mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u c\'f3 ph\u7843 i v\'ec h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u259 n \u273 \u7891  b\'ean ngo\'e0i n\'ean m\u7899 i c\u7889  \'fd g\u7885 i con ma \u273 \'f3 th\u7915 a d\u7883 p giao \u273 \u7891  \u259 n h\'f9 d\u7885 a c\u7853 u hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e2n l\'fac \uc0\u259 n b\u7919 a s\'e1ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i v\u7899 i \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh: "Ch\'fa, con quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh t\u7915  ch\u7913 c t\u7899 i c\'f4ng ty gi\'fap ch\'fa. Ch\'fa h\'e3y tin con trong n\u7917 a th\'e1ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f3 th\u7875  thay \u273 \u7893 i th\u7871  c\u7909 c hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i!" C\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 tin t\'e0 c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'ean m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\u7899 i ch\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n, c\u7853 u v\'ec th\u7853 n tr\u7885 ng n\'ean t\u7921  ti\u7879 n th\'eam v\'e0o m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7891  \u273 \u7891 !" \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh bu\'f4ng \u273 \u361 a xu\u7889 ng ng\u259 n c\u7843 n c\u7853 u. Ng\'e0nh ch\'e1u trai m\'ecnh h\u7885 c c\'f9ng v\u7899 i c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a c\'f4ng ty ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan, n\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat kinh nghi\u7879 m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 giao thi\u7879 p v\'e0 t\'e0i nguy\'ean kh\'e1c, d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\'e1i g\'ec gi\'fap m\'ecnh thay \u273 \u7893 i th\u7871  c\u7909 c. Sao n\'f3 d\'e1m m\u7841 nh mi\u7879 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, quan tr\u7885 ng nh\u7845 t l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3, c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n n\'f3 c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7887  m\u7845 t th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i: "Ch\'fa y\'ean t\'e2m, c\'f4ng vi\uc0\u7879 c hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a con kh\'f4ng gian ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, h\u417 n n\u7919 a ng\'e0nh c\u7911 a con l\u7841 i c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u c\u417  h\u7897 i ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n \u7903  Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883 , sau n\'e0y con c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u7903  l\u7841 i Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883  l\'e0m vi\u7879 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh, n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean con n\'f3i k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch v\'e0 ph\u432 \u417 ng \'e1n c\u7911 a con cho ch\'fa, ch\'fa suy ngh\u297  th\'eam \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng \u7841 ."\cb1 \
