\cb3 M\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u \u272 \u7895  Minh Kinh v\u7851 n ch\u7881  b\u7843 o c\u7853 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat, v\u7873  sau nh\'ecn ra c\u7853 u b\u7843 n l\u297 nh phi th\u432 \u7901 ng, ch\'ednh m\'ecnh v\u7853 y m\'e0 thua xa c\u361 ng li\u7873 n bu\'f4ng tay m\u7863 c k\u7879 . Trong ng\u7921 c th\u7847 m ngh\u297  ti\u7875 u t\u7917  n\'e0y ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n che gi\u7845 u b\u7843 n th\'e2n, th\u7845 y m\'ecnh g\u7863 p n\u7841 n trong l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e0nh l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i b\u7883  k\'edch l\u7897  ra b\u7843 n l\u297 nh th\u7853 t s\u7921 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7873 u ph\u7843 i h\u7887 i \'fd ki\u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, do h\u7855 n \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 o\u7841 t, v\u7873  sau ch\u7853 m r\'e3i h\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, t\u7921  m\'ecnh c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  x\u7917  l\'fd s\u7921  v\u7909  l\u7899 n nh\u7887 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  l\u7899 n m\u7899 i ph\u7843 i b\'e0n b\u7841 c v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\'ed ch\u7845 t c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7915  trong ra ngo\'e0i c\u361 ng kh\'e1c tr\u432 \u7899 c r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n tr\u7903  th\'e0nh *t\'e2n qu\'fd n\u7893 i danh Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883 .\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (T\'e2n qu\'fd: ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i t\'e0i gi\u7887 i \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883  cao m\u7899 i n\u7893 i)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e0 n\'f3i ph\'fa qu\'fd l\u7907 i l\u7897 c c\u361 ng ch\u7881  nh\u432  m\'e2y bay, n\u7871 u nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kh\'e1c chi\u7871 m qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u tinh l\u7921 c v\'e0 l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7855 n c\'f2n kh\'f4ng vui, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh gi\'fap ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau nhanh ch\'f3ng khu\u7871 ch tr\u432 \u417 ng th\u7871  l\u7921 c, \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7921  m\'ecnh ch\u7853 m r\'e3i suy x\'e9t c\u7885  x\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 trong cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  thi\u7871 u xung \u273 \u7897 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ed d\uc0\u7909  nh\u432  m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901  \u273 \'eam Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi \u259 n ti\u7879 c x\'e3 giao xong quay tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u259 n nh\'e0 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 mua \u7903  Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7895  xe \u7903  ga ra, t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a nh\'e0, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai m\u7903  c\u7917 a gi\'fap. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 v\'e0i ph\u7847 n say, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n m\u417  h\u7891  \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7883  kia trong nh\'e0 nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 ang t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n. May m\'e0 h\'f4m nay l\'fac \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i m\'ecnh c\'f3 mang theo ch\'eca kho\'e1.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\u7921  l\u7845 y ch\'eca kho\'e1 m\u7903  c\u7917 a, l\'fac v\u7915 a \u273 i v\'e0o \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i chu\u7849 n b\u7883  b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n l\'ean, \u273 \'e8n tr\u7847 n nguy\'ean b\u7843 n m\'e0u cam gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  phim kinh d\u7883  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ch\u7907 t s\'e1ng ch\u7907 t t\u7889 i, ph\'e1t ra \'e1nh s\'e1ng tr\u7855 ng nh\u7907 t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng d\'f2ng \u273 i\u7879 n x\u7865 t x\u7865 t, chi\u7871 u ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch tr\u7889 ng tr\u7843 i th\'e0nh l\'fac s\'e1ng l\'fac t\u7889 i, h\u7871 t s\u7913 c \'e2m u \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 , t\u7921 a h\u7891  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ch\u7895  n\'e0o \u273 ang \u7849 n gi\u7845 u m\u7897 t u h\u7891 n o\'e1n qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m b\u7883  d\u7885 a s\u7907 . Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 sau b\u7843 y n\u259 m chung s\u7889 ng v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i m\u7845 y th\u7913  n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 l\u7851 m li\u7879 t kh\'f4ng s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  huy\u7873 n quan, v\u7915 a \u273 \u7893 i gi\'e0y v\u7915 a b\'ecnh t\u297 nh n\'f3i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\u7871 u anh l\'e0m h\u432  \u273 \'e8n th\'ec ng\'e0y mai ph\u7843 i thay \u273 \'e8n cho em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7853 t c\'f4ng t\u7855 c n\'e0o \u273 \'f3, ch\u7899 p \u273 \u7897 ng qu\u7927  d\u7883  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t, \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n m\'e0u cam \u7845 m \'e1p chi\u7871 u s\'e1ng to\'e0n b\u7897  ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i tay h\u7919 u l\u7921 c l\u7841 nh bu\u7889 t t\u7915  ph\'eda sau \'f4m l\'ean eo c\u7853 u, h\u417 i th\u7903  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o ph\u7843  v\'e0o c\u7847 n c\u7893 : "Th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng nghe l\u7901 i, h\'f4m nay ph\u7843 i ph\u7841 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u417  hai tay \u273 \u7847 u h\'e0ng, \u273 \'e1p qua loa: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, em sai r\u7891 i, t\'f9y anh ph\u7841 t, ph\u7841 t th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c..."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao c\uc0\u7853 u ph\u7843 n kh\'e1ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843 . D\'f9 sao c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  mu\u7889 n ph\u7843 n kh\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\u7913 t kho\'e1t ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i \'f4m c\u7893  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 u hai nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\u259 n ph\'f2ng lu\'f4n kh\'f3a k\'edn, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n k\u7867  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o, d\'f9 th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\'f3 thu\'ea ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n qu\'e9t d\u7885 n nh\'e0 c\u7917 a th\'ec c\u259 n ph\'f2ng \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  m\u7903  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  sau c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\'ean tr\u7897 m theo d\'f5i c\'e1c h\u7897  gia \u273 \'ecnh trong khu bi\u7879 t th\u7921  n\'e0y, sau m\u7845 y l\u7847 n ra tay thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i li\u7873 n \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t t\u7899 i nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i li\u7873 n tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p leo qua c\u7917 a s\u7893  ph\'f2ng ch\u7913 a \u273 \u7891  l\u7847 u hai \u273 i v\'e0o, \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i sau khi xem qua m\u7897 t v\'f2ng th\'ec nh\u7855 m ngay c\u259 n ph\'f2ng b\u7883  kh\'f3a n\'e0y, c\u7913 ng r\u7855 n c\u7841 y kh\'f3a \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a \u273 i v\'e0o \'97\'97 c\u259 n ph\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e0i tr\'ed th\'e0nh linh \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t b\'e0n th\u7901 , ph\'eda tr\'ean th\u7901  m\u7897 t t\u7845 m b\'e0i v\u7883  m\'e0u \u273 en, ph\'eda tr\'ean c\'f3 s\'e1u ch\u7919  m\'e0u v\'e0ng "Di\u7879 p th\u7883  Ngh\'eanh Chi chi linh"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y h\u7855 n b\u7883  d\u7885 a h\u417 i s\u7907 . Ngay sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i l\u7841 nh nh\u7841 t y\'ean l\u7863 ng h\u7887 i: "Sao l\u7841 i v\'e0o linh \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a ta?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn quanh b\uc0\u7889 n ph\'eda, kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7867  tr\u7897 m cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng t\u7921  m\'ecnh g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'e1o c\u7843 nh s\'e1t k\'eau c\u7843 nh s\'e1t \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f3n m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n th\u7845 y \u273 \u7891 ng ch\'ed c\u7843 nh s\'e1t \u273 \u7871 n l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u432  th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n, kh\'f3c r\u7889 ng h\'f4 c\'f3 qu\u7927 , c\u7847 u b\u7885 n h\u7885  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i mang m\'ecnh \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\u432 ng t\u7909 ng l\'e0 nam nh\'e2n \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n ho\'e0ng kim n\u7893 i danh Th\u7871  Minh th\u7883 , nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ch\u432 a l\u7853 p gia \u273 \'ecnh, kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  ch\u432 a l\u7853 p gia \u273 \'ecnh, th\u7853 m ch\'ed ngay c\u7843  \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng m\u7853 p m\u7901  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng m\u7895 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7871 n th\u7845 t t\u7883 ch, sinh nh\u7853 t hay c\'e1c d\u7883 p \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng h\u7855 n s\u7869  t\'ecm m\u7897 t nh\'e0 h\'e0ng \u432 a th\'edch \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t nh\'e3 gian, b\'e0y hai b\u7897  \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, g\u7885 i hai ph\u7847 n c\u417 m t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u259 n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ch\u7859 ng hi\u7875 u g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  sau c\'f3 nghe \u273 \u7891 n lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng, theo l\u7901 i m\u7897 t b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a Tr\'ec t\u7893 ng \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  ra l\'fac u\u7889 ng say, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau kh\u7855 c c\u7889 t ghi t\'e2m, v\u7873  sau ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 g\u7863 p tai n\u7841 n ngo\'e0i \'fd mu\u7889 n qua \u273 \u7901 i, h\u7855 n li\u7873 n quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7889 ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, c\u361 ng im l\u7863 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i t\'ecnh y\'eau \u273 \'e3 qua n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n c\'e1ch n\'f3i n\u7885 , c\u361 ng th\'e2\u803 t s\u7921  im l\u7863 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n c\u361 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean nguy\'ean nh\'e2n c\u7853 u im l\u7863 ng kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng l\'e0 v\'ec s\u7907  \u273 \u7875  l\u7897 . D\'f9 sao c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t T\u7915  Giang r\'fat cu\u7897 c l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 n\'e3o b\u7893  nh\u7919 ng g\'ec r\u7891 i l\u7841 i k\u7875  v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c ra sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t ra Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y v\'f4 c\'f9ng hoang mang chuy\u7879 n r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c n\'ean c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7843 i qua ng\'e0y k\u7927  ni\u7879 m nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i v\u7899 i t\'ecnh nh\'e2n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 n\'f3i, sinh nh\u7853 t, hai ng\'e0y l\u7877  t\'ecnh nh\'e2n trong n\u432 \u7899 c v\'e0 qu\u7889 c t\u7871 , l\u7877  Gi\'e1ng Sinh, t\u7871 t D\u432 \u417 ng l\u7883 ch, k\u7927  ni\u7879 m ng\'e0y quen bi\u7871 t k\u7927  ni\u7879 m ng\'e0y k\u7871 t h\'f4n g\'ec g\'ec \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t \u273 \u7911  r\u7891 i. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  h\u7855 n ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  sinh nh\u7853 t c\'f2n c\'f3 ng\'e0y gi\u7895 , ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  c\'f9ng h\u7855 n tham gia ng\'e0y l\u7877  nh\'e2n gian c\'f2n c\'f3 *qu\u7927  ti\u7871 t c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7843 i qua.\cb1 \
