\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'ec \uc0\u273 \u7875  b\'e0y t\u7887  t\'ecnh \'fd c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, l\u7877  Vu Lan li\'ean t\u7909 c ba n\u259 m li\u7873 n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7863 t b\'e0n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  nh\'e0 h\'e0ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'edch nh\u7845 t. Khi\u7871 n nh\'e2n vi\'ean ph\u7909 c v\u7909  nh\'e0 h\'e0ng kia \u273 \u7873 u nhao nhao len l\'e9n li\u7871 c c\u7853 u \'97\'97 b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c \u273 \'f3 \u432 ? Tuy r\u7857 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng s\'e2u \u273 \u7853 m \u273 \'e3 qua \u273 \u7901 i... c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c qu\u7927  ti\u7871 t m\u7895 i n\u259 m \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u259 n ph\u7847 n \u259 n c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7875  t\u7871  ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7873 u \u7849 n ch\u7913 a k\'ednh n\u7875  v\'e0 s\u7907  h\'e3i, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\'fac c\u7853 u \u273 i l\u7841 i t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\u361 ng mang theo \'e2m phong, ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 l\'fac mang th\u7913 c \u259 n l\'ean cho c\u7853 u t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u n\u417 m n\u7899 p lo s\u7907 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng kia, trong ng\u7921 c s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 h\'ecnh nh\u432  th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 m\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" \u273 ang ng\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, n\'f3i: "Sau n\'e0y ch\'fang ta c\u7913  v\u7873  nh\'e0 tr\u7843 i qua qu\u7927  ti\u7871 t \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7871 t \'e2m l\u7883 ch n\u259 m nay, ban \u273 \'eam Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e1i xe c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'ean n\'fai l\'e2n c\u7853 n \u273 \u7889 t ph\'e1o hoa.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i tr\u7901 i ph\'e1o hoa r\u7921 c r\u7905  s\'e1ng ch\'f3i, g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'e0ng v\u7841 n \u273 \u7889 m l\u7917 a nh\u7887  chi\u7871 u xu\u7889 ng l\'fac s\'e1ng l\'fac t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\u259 m nay l\'e0 n\u259 m th\u7913  b\u7843 y r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u: "B\u7845 t k\u7875  bao nhi\'eau n\u259 m. Em c\'f2n s\u7889 ng, t\'f4i s\u7869  \u7903  b\'ean em."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n k\'e9o ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c: "A Di\'ean, n\u259 m m\u7899 i vui v\u7867 ."\cb1 \
