\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915  ch\u7889 i tranh lu\u7853 n, h\u432 \u7899 ng ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a h\'f4 m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng "\u272 \u7907 i ch\'fat, t\u7899 i ngay \u273 \'e2y", sau \u273 \'f3 nhanh ch\'f3ng v\u7899  m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c T-shirt v\u7899 i m\u7897 t c\'e1i qu\u7847 n d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t v\u7897 i v\'e0ng m\u7863 c l\'ean, l\u7845 y tay vu\u7889 t vu\u7889 t t\'f3c r\u7891 i ra m\u7903  c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i c\uc0\u7917 a v\u7853 y m\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng g\u7863 p qu\u7927  r\u7891 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 bi\u7871 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \u7871 n cho n\'ean ki\'ean tr\'ec kh\'f4ng ra m\u7903 , mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7907 i t\u7921  c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7903  c\u7917 a?\cb1 \
