\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch h\'ecnh nh\u432  mu\u7889 n v\'e0o ph\'f2ng tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\'ean trong c\'e1nh c\u7917 a l\'e0 b\'f3ng l\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang ng\u7891 i \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n h\u7885 c. B\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n c\'f4 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, em th\u7845 y b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng anh c\u361 ng \u273 ang \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, em kh\'f4ng v\'e0o qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y n\u7919 a, h\'f4m kh\'e1c g\u7863 p l\u7841 i \u7841 ."\cb1 \
