\cb3 Quan h\uc0\u7879  c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a th\'e2n thi\u7871 t \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c h\u7887 i vi\u7879 c t\u432  c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i th\'eam n\u7919 a, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i g\u7863 p b\u7841 n g\'e1i? Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  c\'f3 b\u7841 n g\'e1i \u432 ? H\u7855 n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau s\u7869  l\'e0 d\u7841 ng g\'ec, l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841  kh\'f4ng n\'ean th\'e2n c\u7853 n nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n \'f4n nhu l\'e0m b\u7919 a s\'e1ng... Ngh\u297  t\u7899 i ngh\u297  lui c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m th\u7845 t th\u7847 n, th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi b\u7883  \'e2m b\'e1o tin nh\u7855 n \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i rung l\'ean c\u7855 t ngang m\u7899 i h\u7891 i ph\u7909 c tinh th\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 l\'e3o Vi\'ean h\uc0\u7865 n c\u7853 u bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u \u273 i ch\u417 i b\'f3ng r\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean l\'e0 b\uc0\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng h\u7891 i \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, quan h\u7879  r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'f4i k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u417 i game c\u361 ng l\'e0 h\u7855 n. Sau khi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p h\u7855 n h\u7885 c nghi\'ean c\u7913 u sinh \u7903  \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c B ngay c\u7841 nh, nh\u432 ng Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t n\'e0o c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian r\u7843 nh r\u7895 i v\u7851 n h\u7865 n b\u7841 n h\u7885 c hay ch\u417 i c\'f9ng tr\u432 \u7899 c kia \u273 i ch\u417 i b\'f3ng r\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean vui v\uc0\u7867  \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 a sau khi thay qua qu\u7847 n \'e1o r\u7891 i \u259 n c\u417 m \u7903  nh\'e0 \u259 n xong li\u7873 n ch\u417 i b\'f3ng r\u7893  \u7903  s\'e2n th\u7875  d\u7909 c m\u7897 t bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u c\'f9ng m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n, h\u417 n n\u259 m gi\u7901  m\u7899 i gi\u7843 i t\'e1n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f2n l\uc0\u7841 i l\'e3o Vi\'ean ch\u432 a \u273 i, l\u7847 m b\u7847 m ch\'ea bai n\'f3i c\u417 m nh\'e0 \u259 n \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c B qu\'e1 kh\'f3 \u259 n, *ma l\u7841 t h\u432 \u417 ng oa qu\u7843  th\u7921 c nh\u432  lu\u7897 c ra ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i x\'e0o ra. V\u7851 n l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361  t\u7889 t h\u417 n, c\u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7851 n h\u7855 n \u273 i \u259 n *\u273 \u7891  n\u432 \u7899 ng b\'e0n s\u7855 t v\u7915 a ngon v\u7915 a r\u7867  \u7903  l\u7847 u hai tr\u432 \u7899 c kia h\u7855 n th\'edch nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a \u259 n c\u417 m v\u7915 a t\'e1n d\'f3c, l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\'f3i: "\'c0, Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , b\'e0 x\'e3 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "... T\'f4i ch\uc0\u432 a c\'f3 v\u7907  m\'e0!"\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i n\'f3i C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u7845 y, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\'f4 \u7845 y l\'e0 v\u7907  c\u7853 u trong game \'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 "N\'e0y sao c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0m m\u7897 t..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean im l\u7863 ng, "Game l\'e0 game, b\u7885 n t\'f4i ch\u7881  l\'e0 b\u7841 n b\'e8 b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'f4i, h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng li\'ean l\u7841 c g\'ec." Chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7891  \u259 n s\'e1ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n n\'f3i ra, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 khi l\'e3o Vi\'ean h\u7855 n s\u7869  c\'e0ng n\'e3o b\u7893  th\'eam m\u7855 m th\'eam mu\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean nh\'ecn qua c\uc0\u361 ng r\u7845 t bu\u7891 n b\u7921 c: "V\'ec sao ch\u7913 ? H\'f4m \u273 i g\u7863 p m\u7863 t \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f4 \u7845 y r\u7845 t c\'f3 h\u7843 o c\u7843 m v\u7899 i c\u7853 u. Trong game kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng v\u7851 n r\u7845 t th\'edch c\'f4 \u7845 y sao, b\u7855 n ph\'e1o hoa th\u7913 c \u273 \'eam c\'e0y \u273 \u7891  g\'ec g\'ec \u273 \'f3 cho c\'f4 \u7845 y. Khi \u273 \'f3 b\u7885 n t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u n\'f3i d\'f9 b\'e0 x\'e3 c\u7853 u c\'f3 l\'e0 gay th\'ec c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng tay, b\'e2y gi\u7901  g\u7863 p ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7901 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ti\u7875 u m\u7929  n\u7919  th\'ec ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c..."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i nh\u7887 : "... H\u417 n n\u7919 a t\'f4i th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y hai c\u7853 u r\u7845 t c\'f3 duy\'ean m\'e0, c\'f4 \u7845 y t\'ean Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh c\u361 ng h\u417 i gi\u7889 ng c\u7853 u..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i g\'ec?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean khi\u7871 p s\u7907  qu\'ean \u259 n, bu\'f4ng \u273 \u361 a xu\u7889 ng ch\u7881  v\'e0o m\u361 i m\'ecnh, "C\u7853 u n\'f3i t\'f4i v\u7899 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh gi\u7889 ng nhau?" C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch ch\u7895  n\'e0o c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t ti\u7875 u m\u7929  nh\'e2n, ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh th\u7853 t v\u7899 i nh\'e2n v\u7853 t trong game gi\u7889 ng nhau, sao c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7889 ng m\'ecnh?\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean xua xua tay: "\'c2y, Th\uc0\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867  c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng, C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch v\u7899 i c\u7853 u k\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng l\u7855 m. T\'f4i l\'e0 n\'f3i nh\'e2n v\u7853 t 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i " c\'f4 \u7845 y t\u7841 o ra trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i k\'eca, m\u7863 c d\'f9 m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra c\'f4 \u7845 y d\u7921 a theo m\u7863 t m\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  t\u7841 o nh\'e2n v\u7853 t, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 v\'e0o game x\'e2y d\u7921 ng h\'ecnh m\u7851 u xong, m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3, mi\u7879 ng \u273 \'f3, li\u7873 n... c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t gi\u7889 ng c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t m\'ea mang, ho\'e0n to\'e0n nghe kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i n\u7919 a, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng l\u7845 y c\u7899  mua \u273 \u7891  u\u7889 ng cho hai ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 n, sau khi mua \u273 \u7891  v\u7873  li\u7873 n d\u7851 n d\u7855 t l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 \u7893 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7873  \u273 \u7875  h\u7855 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c than th\u7903  v\u7873  nh\'e0 \u259 n \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c B.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi ti\uc0\u7877 n l\'e3o Vi\'ean r\u7901 i \u273 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t m\'ecnh tr\u7903  v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1, l\'ean m\u7841 ng nghe nh\u7841 c m\u7897 t l\'fac xong b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901  \u273 \'eam.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i ng\'e0y mai l\'e0 ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t, \u273 ang \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \'eam nay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7859 n l\'e0 kh\'f4ng v\u7873  n\u7919 a, ch\u7907 t nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng ch\'eca kho\'e1 tra v\'e0o \u7893  m\u7903  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7917 a "c\u7841 ch.." m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng b\u7883  \u273 \u7849 y ra, Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'e1o tai nghe quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, th\u7845 y b\'f3ng d\'e1ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, c\u7903 i \'e1o ngo\'e0i treo l\'ean t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o, quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang ng\u417  ng\'e1c nh\'ecn m\'ecnh ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \u273 i qua, \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng: "L\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 c\u7913  nh\'ecn t\'f4i v\u7853 y? Sao c\'f2n ch\u432 a ng\u7911 ?" Nh\u7899  t\'f4i \'e0? Ba ch\u7919  cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng g\u7847 n nh\u432  s\u7855 p th\u7889 t ra, l\u7841 i b\u7883  h\u7855 n nu\u7889 t tr\u7903  v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7917 a \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "Sao kh\'f4ng v\u7873  nh\'e0 m\'e0 l\u7841 i quay l\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi "\u7914 m" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "G\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng an to\'e0n l\u7855 m, t\'f4i s\u7869  \u7903  l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng. Bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\u7889  g\u7855 ng v\u7873  s\u7899 m m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng an to\'e0n l\uc0\u7855 m?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 ang mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i, ch\u7907 t th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\'f3t m\u7897 t c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915  ch\u7895  b\'ecnh l\u7885 c r\u7891 i ng\u7891 i tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, c\u7903 i hai c\'fac \'e1o s\u417  mi tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, sau \u273 \'f3 c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u v\u7915 a c\u7903 i c\'fac tay \'e1o v\u7915 a b\'ecnh th\u7843 n n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u ch\u432 a nghe n\'f3i sao? V\u7915 a r\u7891 i \u7903  hai \u273 \u7847 u ph\u7889  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t, m\u7855 t tr\u7907 n l\u7899 n, b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'f3c tim c\u7855 t l\u432 \u7905 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7843  kinh, m\u7903  to m\u7855 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. \u272 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i ch\'ednh di\u7879 n l\'e0 \u273 \'f4i \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7917  m\'e0u \u273 en y\'ean l\u7863 ng s\'e2u kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e1y c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
