\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh v\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 th\u7875  d\'f9ng gi\u7885 ng \u273 i\u7879 u v\'e0 bi\u7875 u l\u7897  b\'ecnh t\u297 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u7875  k\u7875  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n ch\'e2n th\u7921 c th\u7871  n\'e0y. T\'ecnh c\u7843 nh n\u7885  c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\u7847 n t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng r\'e9t m\'e0 run. Nh\u432 ng l\u7841  l\'e0 th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432  v\u7853 y ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i tr\u7845 n an c\u7853 u, khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c qu\'e1 th\u7845 t th\u7889 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u ph\u7889  ch\u7881  c\'e1ch tr\u432 \u7901 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7897 t tr\u7841 m t\'e0u \u273 i\u7879 n ng\u7847 m, t\u7917  tr\u7841 ng th\'ea th\u7843 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  khi\u7871 n m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'e0n t\'e1n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Theo tin t\uc0\u7913 c \u273 \u7891 n \u273 \u7841 i c\u7911 a b\u7841 n h\u7885 c, ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t l\'e0 c\'f4 g\'e1i b\'e1n \u273 \u7891  trang \u273 i\u7875 m trong trung t\'e2m mua s\u7855 m Li\'ean Hoa \u7903  hai \u273 \u7847 u ph\u7889 , h\'f4m nay tr\u7921 c ca \u273 \'eam, trung t\'e2m mua s\u7855 m m\u7903  c\u7917 a \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  t\u7889 i, h\u417 n m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901  m\u7899 i c\'f4 tan l\'e0m \u273 i ra \u273 \'e1p t\'e0u \u273 i\u7879 n ng\u7847 m, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i l\u7847 n n\'e0y v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i g\u7863 p b\u7845 t tr\u7855 c. B\u7903 i v\'ec t\u7917  tr\u7841 ng th\'ea th\u7843 m qu\u7927  d\u7883 , hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 phong t\u7887 a tin t\u7913 c, loa c\'f4ng c\u7897 ng ch\u7881  ph\'e1t th\'f4ng b\'e1o nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  c\u432  d\'e2n xung quanh ch\'fa \'fd an to\'e0n, kh\'f4ng n\'ean v\u7873  mu\u7897 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u ph\u7889  bu\'f4n b\'e1n s\u7847 m u\u7845 t, \u7903  g\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c, sinh vi\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c A \u273 \u7873 u th\'edch v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 \u259 n u\u7889 ng mua s\u7855 m, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng \u273 i qua n\u417 i x\u7843 y ra v\u7909  \'e1n, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f2n t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p qua ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i \u7903  trong trung t\'e2m mua s\u7855 m. Trong \u273 \u7847 u x\u7865 t qua t\'e1m ch\u7919  "Ch\u7871 t kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, m\'f3c tim c\u7855 t l\u432 \u7905 i", Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i run r\u7849 y, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ngh\u297  ti\u7871 p n\u7919 a, n\'f3i ch\'fac ng\u7911  ngon v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi xong li\u7873 n l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'fac n\uc0\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  c\'f3 tr\u7897 m? Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7913 , ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u \u7903  l\u7847 u s\'e1u c\u417  m\'e0...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn qua n\u417 i ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng, xuy\'ean qua c\u7917 a s\u7893  tho\'e1ng th\u7845 y lan can ngo\'e0i ban c\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i. C\u7853 u h\u417 i thanh t\u7881 nh, m\u7903  to m\u7855 t nh\'ecn \'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7863 c v\'e1y n\u7919  m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  s\u7853 m \u273 ang ng\u7891 i tr\'ean lan can, nh\'ecn ch\'f2ng ch\u7885 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean, trong \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\u7903  l\u7899 n ph\u7911  k\'edn t\u417  m\'e1u. H\'ecnh nh\u432  n\'f3 mu\u7889 n n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3, h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng, trong mi\u7879 ng tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u432 \u7905 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t ra thanh \'e2m "T\'ea t\'ea...\'ea...eeee".\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c d\u7901 i xu\u7889 ng nh\'ecn ph\u7847 n ng\u7921 c c\u7911 a n\'f3, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c b\u7883  kho\'e9t m\u7897 t l\u7895  l\u7899 n, c\'f3 th\u7875  lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e1u th\u7883 t m\u417  h\u7891  v\u7899 i ru\u7897 t b\u7909 ng l\'f2i ra...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng th\u7903  n\u7893 i, trong gi\'e2y l\'e1t h\u7889 t ho\u7843 ng c\u7853 u nh\u7899  ra h\'f4m nay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, \'fd ngh\u297  n\'e0y v\u7915 a hi\u7879 n l\'ean trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 k\'eau l\'ean: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi! Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e0m sao v\uc0\u7853 y? G\u7863 p \'e1c m\u7897 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i b\'ecnh t\u297 nh \'f4n h\'f2a c\u7911 a b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng, l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i d\'e1m m\u7903  to m\u7855 t, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  n\u7919 a m\'e0 nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, \u273 ang b\'ecnh t\u297 nh nh\'ecn c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nu\u7889 t nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng, l\u7845 y tay ch\u7881  ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  theo bi\'ean \u273 \u7897  nh\u7887 , th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... C\u7853 u xem b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f4ng..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i, quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec c\u7843 . C\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u g\u7863 p \'e1c m\u7897 ng kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i x\'e1c nh\u7853 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, m\u7899 i h\u7841  quy\u7871 t t\'e2m t\u7921  m\'ecnh quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn l\u7841 i, ban c\'f4ng tr\u7889 ng tr\u417 n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o h\'f4m qua m\'ecnh ph\u417 i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a thu v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... T\'f4i v\uc0\u7915 a th\u7845 y b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7919 , m\u7863 c v\'e1y \u273 \u7887 , kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y n\u7917 a ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7899 i. C\'f4 ta c\'f2n nh\'ecn t\'f4i, h\'ecnh nh\u432  mu\u7889 n n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3... Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\'f4 ta \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  c\u7855 t l\u432 \u7905 i, m\'f3c tim." N\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n ph\u7847 n sau c\u7853 u l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng d\'e2ng l\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn nh\'ecn.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'e2u, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 h\'f4m nay nghe th\u7845 y tin kia b\u7883  d\u7885 a s\u7907  n\'ean sinh ra \u7843 o gi\'e1c r\u7891 i, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 ng\u7911  m\u417  t\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7853 t. \u272 \u7915 ng ngh\u297  n\u7919 a, ng\u7911  \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n qu\u7927  th\u7847 n chung quy lu\'f4n huy\u7873 n di\u7879 u kh\'f3 gi\u7843 i th\'edch, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n c\'f3 ch\'fat ngh\u297  l\u7841 i m\'e0 s\u7907 , nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng ng\u7841 i bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n qu\'e1 nh\'e1t gan v\'f4 d\u7909 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng, ch\u7881  m\u7899 i nghe n\'f3i m\u7897 t v\u7909  \'e1n gi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  d\u7885 a \u273 \u7871 n hoang mang lo s\u7907 . V\'ec v\u7853 y c\u361 ng g\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong th\uc0\u7901 i gian ng\u7855 n ng\u7911  s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i th\'ec c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i s\u7869  hi\u7879 n l\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t. N\u7917 a \u273 \'eam canh ba Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ti\u7879 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c l\'e0m phi\u7873 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  m\'ecnh c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i y\'ean l\u7863 ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang nh\'ecn m\'ecnh, h\u417 n n\u7919 a \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3 h\'ecnh nh\u432  t\u7899 i t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i ban c\'f4ng...\cb1 \
\
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 n n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta v\u7915 a m\u7899 i ng\u7911 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n l\u7841 i \u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\u7847 n hai; nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng x\'e1c nh\u7853 n th\'ec l\u7841 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  ho\u7843 ng s\u7907 , kh\'f4ng an t\'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Do d\uc0\u7921  c\u7843  bu\u7893 i, suy \u273 i t\'ednh l\u7841 i, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 ng gan l\'ean l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  \'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia to\'e9t c\'e1i mi\u7879 ng kh\'f4ng l\u432 \u7905 i, h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u l\u7897  ra n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\'f4, c\u7853 u v\u7915 a b\'f2 v\u7915 a l\u7871 t xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, to\'e0n t\'e2m to\'e0n \'fd ng\u7855 m chu\u7849 n x\'e1c gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, li\u7871 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m li\u7871 c ch\u7895  kh\'e1c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  n\u7855 m c\u7885 ng c\u7887  c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng b\'f2 l\'ean b\u7853 c thang gi\u432 \u7901 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, b\u7855 t l\u7845 y ch\u259 n h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t phen \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng t\u7881 nh, h\u7855 n m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "L\u7841 i sao th\u7871 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ra l\u7901 i, th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n m\u7845 y h\u417 i m\u7899 i n\u417 m n\u7899 p lo s\u7907  m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "... Th\u7913  kia v\u7851 n \u7903  ngo\'e0i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay c\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng run r\u7849 y, xem ra qu\u7843  th\u7921 c s\u7855 p kh\'f3c l\'ean r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7883 ch v\'e0o trong, t\u7915  tr\'ean xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i ng\u7855 m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c qu\u7847 n \u273 \'f9i th\'ec c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n tr\u7847 n tr\u7909 i, h\u7855 n v\u7895  v\u7895  ch\u259 n: "Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean l\'ean \u273 \'e2y \u273 i, \u7903  ngo\'e0i l\u7841 nh." B\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 cu\u7889 i th\'e1ng m\u432 \u7901 i, nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  ph\u432 \u417 ng b\u7855 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng cao, m\u7897 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\'e1y s\u432 \u7903 i hai kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u h\'f2a, c\u7853 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 \u7913 ng tr\'ean thang nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 khi s\u7869  c\u7843 m m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u432  nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7855 c l\u7879 nh n\'e0o \u273 \'f3, nhanh ch\'f3ng b\'f2 l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n t\u7915 ng ch\'fat m\u7897 t k\'e9o m\u7897 t g\'f3c ch\u259 n ph\u7911  l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quay \u273 \u7847 u v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7917 a s\u7893  nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua: "V\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec c\u7843 . Ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n l\'e0 c\u7853 u nh\'ecn l\u7847 m r\u7891 i, t\u7921  m\'ecnh d\u7885 a m\'ecnh."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\'f3 n\'f3i g\'ec th\'ec Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7857 m d\u7883 ch v\'e0o trong t\u432 \u7901 ng: "Ng\u7911  \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y c\u7911 a t\'f4i \u273 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\u7845 y ch\u259 n qua \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'e3, ch\u7895  t\'f4i ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'f2ng c\'f2n s\uc0\u7907  h\'e3i, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n gi\u432 \u7901 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 d\'f9ng h\u7871 t to\'e0n b\u7897  kh\'ed l\u7921 c, \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  hai ch\'e2n v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 ang run r\u7849 y. C\u7853 u nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u273 \'f4\u803 ng, ng\u7849 n ng\u417  ng\u7891 i \u7903  \u273 \'f3, tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn c\'f3 ch\'fat \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7845 c m\u7897 t g\'f3c ch\u259 n l\'ean: "V\'e0o \u273 \'e2y ng\u7911  \u273 i, tr\u7901 i s\u7855 p s\'e1ng r\u7891 i, ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i do d\u7921 , chui v\'e0o, \u273 \u7847 u ti\u7871 n l\u7841 i g\u7847 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i "C\u7843 m \u417 n" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng trong k\'ed t\'fac c\u361 ng ch\u7881  r\u7897 ng m\u7897 t m\'e9t, hai nam thanh ni\'ean chen ch\'fac th\u7853 t s\u7921  mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng. C\u7843  hai ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7911 , l\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i l\u432 ng, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng y\'ean \u7893 n v\'f4 s\u7921 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'eam nay Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7883 u kinh h\'e3i li\'ean t\u7909 c qu\'e1 l\u7899 n, tinh th\u7847 n c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng, sau khi th\u7843  l\u7887 ng r\u7845 t nhanh li\u7873 n ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau l\'fac m\uc0\u7903  m\u7855 t ra c\u7853 u th\u7845 y trong ph\'f2ng \u273 \'e3 s\'e1ng, tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng h\'edt th\u7903  kh\'e1c. C\u7853 u h\u417 i quay \u273 \u7847 u, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i t\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o, \u273 \u7847 u d\u7921 a tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u, c\'e1nh tay ph\u7843 i c\u361 ng kho\'e1c h\u7871 t l\'ean l\u432 ng c\u7853 u, th\'e2n th\u7875  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i k\u7873  s\'e1t, b\'e0y ra tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi bao quanh c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e0ng th\'eam l\'fang t\'fang ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\'f3 th\uc0\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 ang v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\'f4 l\'ean c\u7885  \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\'e1 to mi\uc0\u7879 ng, ng\'e2y ng\u432 \u7901 i trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 i qua \u273 \'e3 qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y l\'e0m phi\u7873 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u, khi\u7871 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y gi\u7901 , l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 t s\u7921  ng\u7841 i \u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c h\u7855 n. C\u7853 u th\u7917  thay \u273 \u7893 i t\u432  th\u7871  v\u7883  tr\'ed c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, t\u7915  t\u7915  nh\'edch ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec kh\'f4ng gian th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 h\u7841 n, tay ph\u7843 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e8 c\u7853 u l\u7841 i ch\u7863 t, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7853 u \u273 ang ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng ngh\'eanh h\u7907 p h\u7847 u h\u7841  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7863 t ngh\u7865 n \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7855 n r\u259 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1i, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh gi\u7843  b\u7897  kh\'f4ng hay kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao... kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u s\uc0\u7869  h\u7871 t th\'f4i nh\u7881 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec s\'e1ng s\u7899 m b\u7843 n th\'e2n gi\u7843  b\u7897  l\'e0m nh\u432  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f2n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng v\'f4 th\u7913 c ph\'e1t sinh s\u7921  c\u7889  kia, c\'f9ng v\u7899 i t\u7889 i qua ch\'ednh m\'ecnh qu\'e1 kinh s\u7907  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta v\u432 \u7899 ng th\'eam kh\'f4ng \'edt phi\u7873 n to\'e1i, ch\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n khi Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, v\'e0nh tai \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7903 \'a0 m\u7855 t, v\u7915 a n\'e2ng c\'e1nh tay l\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c n\'f3i: "Th\u7853 t xin l\u7895 i, c\'f3 \u273 \'e8 l\'ean c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec k\u7873  s\'e1t, tai v\'e0 c\u7893  \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhanh ch\'f3ng l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, l\u7855 c v\'e0i c\'e1i l\u7841 i b\u7893  sung: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3. H\u7843 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3, ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua c\u7843 m \u417 n c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u417 i cong \'e1nh m\u7855 t, b\u7897  d\'e1ng c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\u432 \u7901 i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec. \u272 \u7915 ng nghi th\u7847 n nghi qu\u7927  t\u7921  m\'ecnh d\u7885 a m\'ecnh n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y l\'e0m g\'ec c\'f3 qu\u7927 . \u272 \u7873 u l\'e0 th\'eau d\u7879 t ra g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\
