\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7911  nh\u7853 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  th\u432  vi\u7879 n xem lu\u7853 n v\u259 n m\u7897 t ng\'e0y, \u259 n t\u7889 i xong m\u7899 i quay v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7853 u v\u7851 n th\u7845 y v\u7915 a x\u7845 u h\u7893  v\u7915 a ng\u7841 i, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\'ecn ra kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u l\u7855 p b\u7855 p n\'f3i: "H\'f4m nay v\u7873 , v\u7873  s\u7899 m ha." Sau \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n tr\u7889 n \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  b\'e0n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh quay l\u432 ng l\u7841 i ph\'eda h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i s\'e1ng c\u7853 u v\u7889 n ngh\u297  th\u7901 i gian s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\'e2u \u273 \'e2u, r\u7845 t nhanh s\u7869  h\u7871 t, r\u7845 t nhanh s\u7869  qua th\'f4i, nh\u432 ng, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 k\u7871 t qu\u7843  l\'e0 th\u7901 i gian th\u7853 t d\'e0i m\u7899 i h\u7871 t... C\u7843  ng\'e0y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7885 c kinh t\u7871  h\u7885 c c\u7893  \u273 i\u7875 n tu th\'e2n d\u432 \u7905 ng t\'ednh, th\'f4i mi\'ean b\u7843 n th\'e2n "Ta l\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  ng\u7911  c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t", nh\u432 ng m\'e0 ch\u7881  c\u7847 n h\u417 i ch\'fat ngh\u297  t\u7899 i, l\u7841 i v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7899  l\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'f3...\cb1 \
\cb3 Vi\uc0\u7871 t l\'e1ch t\u7855 m r\u7917 a xong Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\'f2 l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng xem \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, t\'ecnh h\'ecnh c\u7909  th\u7875  v\u7909  th\u7843 m \'e1n ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  phong t\u7887 a nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\'f3 kh\'f4ng \'edt l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n \u273 \u7841 i truy\u7873 n ra, c\u7853 u v\'f4 th\u7913 c l\u432 \u7907 c qua t\u7845 t c\u7843  kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n ti\u7871 p x\'fac \'97\'97 chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'eam qua qu\u7843  th\u7921 c \u7903  \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i b\'f3ng ma qu\'e1 s\'e2u cho c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  kia l\'e0 th\u7853 t hay gi\u7843 , l\'e0 m\u7897 ng hay l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7879 n tay \u7845 n m\u7903  m\u7897 t lo\u7841 t tin nh\u7855 n tr\'ean \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 nh\'f3m mua kh\u7849 u trang hoa qu\u7843  giao h\'e0ng t\u7853 n n\u417 i n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u b\u7883  b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c k\'e9o v\'e0o, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  trong ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n l\'e0 sinh vi\'ean \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c xung quanh, nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u quen bi\u7871 t c\u361 ng ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n hai ba ng\u432 \u7901 i, mua kh\u7849 u trang xong c\u361 ng qu\'ean tho\'e1t, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i t\u7855 t \'e2m, chung quy lu\'f4n v\'f4 th\u7913 c kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd. Kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'eam nay l\u7841 i \u7845 n m\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'f3m c\'f3 g\uc0\u7917 i m\u7897 t t\u7845 m h\'ecnh, tr\'ean h\'ecnh l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'f4 g\'e1i m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i, ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n n\'f3i "\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i h\'f4m qua, c\'f2n r\u7845 t xinh \u273 \u7865 p, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 b\u7883  nh\u432  v\u7853 y" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhanh ch\'f3ng n\u7893 i l\'ean \'e1nh m\u7855 t g\u7855 t gao nh\'ecn m\'ecnh ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m n\u7885 , l\u7895  th\u7911 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, v\'e0 c\'e1i mi\u7879 ng tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng t\u432 \u417 i c\u432 \u7901 i h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh...\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai tay c\uc0\u7853 u run r\u7849 y, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c n\'e9m di \u273 \u7897 ng l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7851 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i qu\u7927  m\'e0 nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m v\'e0o c\'f4 g\'e1i n\'e9t m\u7863 t c\u432 \u7901 i t\u432 \u417 i nh\u432  hoa tr\'ean m\'e0n h\'ecnh. M\u7897 t l\'e1t sau m\u7899 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, quay \u273 \u7847 u chuy\u7875 n h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng v\u7851 n \u273 ang ng\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n s\'e1ch b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "L\'e0m sao v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Bao gi\uc0\u7901  c\u361 ng l\'e0 b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh t\u7921  nhi\'ean mang \u273 \u7871 n s\u7921  y\'ean t\'e2m v\'f4 c\'f9ng. C\u7853 u c\u7889  g\u7855 ng m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a nh\u7863 t di \u273 \u7897 ng l\'ean gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\u7863 t con b\u7885  c\u7841 p, ch\u7881  cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i: "... \u272 \'eam qua t\'f4i th\u7845 y ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\'e1i n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u259 n v\'e0o x\u432 \u417 ng, trong l\'f2ng l\u7841 i c\'e0ng sinh ra t\u7915 ng tia \u7899 n l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e1c \uc0\u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i v\u7853 t ch\u7845 t quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh \'fd th\u7913 c. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y c\u7853 u ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i, n\u7871 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\u7853 n m\u7855 t nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, \u273 \'eam qua l\'e0m sao l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u259 n c\u7913  m\'e0 t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7897  d\'e1ng sau khi ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\u7897 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u7843 o gi\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 en s\u7851 m, mang theo s\u7907  s\u7879 t kh\'f4ng th\u7875  che gi\u7845 u, m\'f4i h\u417 i run run, th\u7853 m ch\'ed s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7853 n \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua, l\u7841 i nh\'ecn b\u7897  d\'e1ng l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean. H\u7855 n \u273 \'f3ng nh\'f3m chat l\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i hai l\u7901 i tr\'e8o l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i d\u7921 a v\'e0o ph\'eda ngo\'e0i, \u7845 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng c\'f9ng h\u7855 n: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u7915 ng ngh\u297  n\u7919 a, c\'f2n c\'f3 t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y. B\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c \u273 i, ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i cho t\u7889 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i cao ng\u7845 t c\u432 \u7901 ng ki\u7879 n, ng\u259 n \u7903  b\'ean ngo\'e0i t\u7921 a nh\u432  ho\'e0n to\'e0n che khu\u7845 t b\u7843 o v\u7879  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7899 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\'fat c\u7843 m gi\'e1c an to\'e0n, ng\u417  ng\'e1c thu\u7853 n theo n\u7857 m \u7903  trong, l\'fang t\'fang kinh ho\u7843 ng l\'fac s\'e1ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  n\'e9m l\'ean ch\'edn t\u7847 ng m\'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7845 c ch\u259 n l\'ean b\u7885 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o, suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng chui v\'e0o, kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\uc0\u7857 m quay v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng quay m\u7863 t v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, tay kho\'e1c l\'ean vai c\u7853 u, l\u7841 i nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng l\u7863 p l\u7841 i: "Ng\u7911  \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y hay kh\'f4ng, l\'e1t sau tho\'e1ng b\'ecnh t\u297 nh xu\u7889 ng m\u7899 i l\u7841 i nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "C\u7843 m \u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i s\'e1ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 qu\u7927 , c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng h\u7873  tin nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c m\'ecnh \u259 n n\'f3i l\u7843 m nh\u7843 m kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7845 t c\u7913  ch\u7913 ng c\u7913  g\'ec h\u7855 n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  x\'ec m\u361 i coi th\u432 \u7901 ng hay b\u7887  m\u7863 c, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i r\u7845 t ki\'ean nh\u7851 n \u273 \u7897 ng vi\'ean m\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  m\'ecnh bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng tinh th\u7847 n. Trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u c\'e0ng \u273 \u432 a ra k\u7871 t lu\u7853 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7889 t trong n\'f3ng ngo\'e0i l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m sau l\'e0 th\uc0\u7913  hai, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 l\u7899 p chuy\'ean ng\'e0nh bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng, t\u7915  9:50 \u273 \u7871 n 11:25, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'ec c\u7843  ng\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u7899 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7911  ph\'eda trong, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'e1o th\u7913 c v\u7915 a vang l\'ean, c\u7853 u kh\u7869  \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1i c\u7843  hai li\u7873 n t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y.\'a0 C\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \'e1o s\u417 mi h\u417 i nh\u259 n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i \u7903  c\u7841 nh b\u7891 i m\'ecnh c\u7843  \u273 \'eam, c\'f3 ch\'fat c\u7843 m \u273 \u7897 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7917  m\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "\u7914 m... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a c\u7853 u c\'f3 l\u7883 ch g\'ec kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi nh\uc0\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1p \'e1n ph\u7911  \u273 \u7883 nh, c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c n\'f3i: "T\'f4i m\u7901 i c\u7853 u \u259 n c\u417 m nh\'e9?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi li\u7871 c c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "T\u7921  c\u7853 u l\'e0m?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i, " Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\'ean t\u7909 c xua tay, "\u258 n b\'ean ngo\'e0i... T\'f4i ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t n\u7845 u m\'ec g\'f3i th\'f4i." Hu\u7889 ng chi trong tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p n\u7845 u c\u417 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n l\u7901 i kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921 , m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng cao l\'e3nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7899 p chuy\'ean ng\'e0nh s\'e1ng nay l\'e0 m\'f4n b\u7855 t bu\u7897 c c\u7911 a khoa kinh t\u7871 , cho n\'ean l\u432 \u7907 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i xem nh\u432  t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i nhi\u7873 u, h\u7885 c \u7903  m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng l\u7899 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh b\u7841 n c\'f9ng l\u7899 p D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh, b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u l\u7841 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh l\u7863 ng l\u7869  ch\u7885 t ch\u7885 t c\u7853 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh \u273 \'fang l\'e0 C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch th\u7845 y c\u7853 u li\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ch\'e0o bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng, em t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y h\u7885 c k\'e9."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng l\'fang t\'fang g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Ch\'e0o bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean nh\'e1y m\u7855 t ra hi\u7879 u cho c\u7853 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\u7843  b\u7897  chuy\'ean t\'e2m xem gi\'e1o tr\'ecnh, coi nh\u432  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac ngh\uc0\u7881  gi\u7919 a gi\u7901  D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u273 i v\u7879  sinh, ra t\u7899 i h\'e0nh lang D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh li\u7873 n \u273 \u7853 p vai c\u7853 u: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u gia, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7847 u g\u7895  nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7913 ? Ti\u7875 u m\u7929  n\u7919  khoa Anh v\u259 n kia r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 th\'edch c\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7901 i ta \u273 \'e2u c\'f3 t\u7899 i h\u7885 c k\'e9, r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n v\'ec c\u7853 u. C\u7853 u \u273 \'fang l\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \'e1nh m\u7855 t nh\u7887  \u273 \'f3 nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, theo kinh nghi\u7879 m c\u7911 a t\'f4i, \u273 \'e2y tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i l\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  th\'edch, kh\'f4ng gi\u7843  b\u7897  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u \u273 i, c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "N\u7871 u c\u7853 u th\'edch th\'ec t\'f4i gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u gi\'fap c\u7853 u nh\'e9."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh lui m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c: "\u272 \u432 \u768 ng \u273 \u432 \u768 ng \u273 \u7915 ng, \u273 \u7915 ng c\'f3 n\'f3i b\u7915 a, b\u7841 n g\'e1i t\'f4i nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao." Sau \u273 \'f3 v\'ec \u273 \u7875  ch\u7913 ng minh b\u7843 n th\'e2n trong s\u7841 ch li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tan h\uc0\u7885 c C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch l\u7841 i xoay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t s\'e1ng thi\u7879 n l\u432 \u417 ng nghi\'eang nghi\'eang, c\u432 \u7901 i t\u432 \u417 i: "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a ch\'fang ta c\'f9ng \u259 n c\u417 m \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\'f3i: "Bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a t\'f4i c\'f3 h\u7865 n r\u7891 i. Hay l\'e0 m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i\'a0 \u273 i \u259 n c\'f9ng \u273 i?" N\'f3i xong c\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh d\'f9ng m\u7855 t h\u7887 i. D\'f9 sao \u273 \'fang l\'e0 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 m\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, d\u7851 n th\'eam hai b\u7841 n h\u7885 c t\u7899 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao h\u7871 t. Th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t c\'f3 h\u417 i t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ta, c\u7853 u c\u7889  \'fd nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh, n\'f3i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng \u273 i \u259 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 v\'ec kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch hi\u7875 u l\u7847 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh l\'e0 b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t th\'e2n thi\u7871 t, nghe c\u7853 u m\u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec \u273 \'e1p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\u361 ng d\u7883 u d\'e0ng g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i t\u7921 a nh\u432  thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng h\u7887 i: "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, anh h\u7865 n ai th\u7871 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec, l\'e0 b\uc0\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. C\u7853 u ta... \u273 \'e3 gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  anh." Tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e3 qua m\u7897 t ng\'e0y, nh\u432 ng nh\u7899  t\u7899 i s\u7921  c\u7889  sau \u273 \'f3 v\u7851 n c\'f3 ch\'fat nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 x\u226 \u769 u h\'f4\u777 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901 . R\u7845 t nhanh c\'f4 \u273 i\u7873 u ch\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, m\u7897 t b\u7897  d\'e1ng v\u7915 a nh\u7899  ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'f3: "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7853 t l\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang d\u7883 p. Em v\u7915 a nh\u7899  ra \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng \u273 i gi\'fap Gi\u7843 n Doanh l\'e0m m\u7845 y vi\u7879 c r\u7891 i... Kh\'f4ng \u273 i c\'f9ng c\'e1c anh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\u7847 n sau em m\u7901 i anh l\u7841 i nh\'e9?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\uc0\u7899 i kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, trong ng\u7921 c r\u7891 i l\u7841 i \'e2m th\u7847 m th\u7903  ph\'e0o nh\u7865  nh\'f5m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean \u7903  chung v\u7899 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o cho th\u7887 a \u273 \'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac c\uc0\u7853 u v\'e0 D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 h\'e0ng th\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh c\u7917 a s\u7893  m\u7897 t nh\'e3 gian, tay \'e1o s\u417 mi h\u417 i x\u7855 n l\'ean, \u273 ang v\'f4 c\'f9ng bu\u7891 n ch\'e1n nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 . Nh\u432 ng m\u7897 t kh\u7855 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a \u273 i v\'e0o h\u7855 n l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u, c\u432 \u7901 i h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u v\u7851 y tay ch\'e0o h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng n\'e0y c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 gi\u7889 ng t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Th\u7853 t ra ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh v\'e0 kh\'ed ch\u7845 t so v\u7899 i trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t th\'ec v\u7851 n \u273 \u7891 ng nh\u7845 t, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7891 ng nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 b\u7889 n chai r\u432 \u7907 u b\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t h\u7855 n, m\u7897 t chai r\u432 \u7907 u tr\u7855 ng, m\u7897 t chai r\u432 \u7907 u vang, c\'f2n c\'f3 hai chai bia \'97\'97 ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng nghe c\'f3 ai \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng m\u7901 i \u259 n, trong khi ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\'f2n ch\u432 a t\u7899 i th\'ec b\u7843 n th\'e2n tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 g\u7885 i m\u7897 t lo\u7841 t c\'e1c lo\u7841 i r\u432 \u7907 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7899 i thi\u7879 u hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i nhau, sau khi \u273 \u7891  \u259 n l\'ean Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi li\u7873 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \'e2n c\u7847 n m\u7901 i r\u432 \u7907 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c xa l\u7841  trong l\'f2ng D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh l\u7841 i t\u259 ng th\'eam, b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng ch\u7881  \'e2n c\u7847 n v\u7899 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh Tr\'ec Di\'ean. H\u7855 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng l\'e0m ch\u7911  trong nh\'e0, phong \u273 \u7897  nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i h\'e0o ph\'f3ng m\u7901 i D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh c\u7913  t\u7921  nhi\'ean, sau \u273 \'f3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh r\'f3t r\u432 \u7907 u m\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'97\'97 v\'e0i lo\u7841 i r\u432 \u7907 u h\'f2a chung v\u7899 i nhau, r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 k\u7871 t c\u7845 u g\'ec, h\u7855 n l\u7841 i n\'f3i l\'e0 tuy\u7879 t k\u7929  pha ch\u7871  r\u432 \u7907 u \u273 \u7897 c m\'f4n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, k\'eau Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i n\u7871 m th\u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "U\u7889 ng l\u7851 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y... kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 ?" C\'f3 ai pha ch\u7871  r\u432 \u7907 u nh\u432  th\u7871  \u432 ? R\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mang theo ti\u7871 u \'fd th\u7843 n nhi\'ean nh\'ecn h\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh t\u7921  nh\u7911  trong l\'f2ng ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  v\u7883  Di\u7879 p c\'f4ng t\u7917  n\'e0y l\u7841 i l\'e0 *s\'e1t th\u7909 c? Th\'e2n thu\u7897 c v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, li\u7873 n t\u259 ng c\u432 \u7901 ng gi\'e0y v\'f2 c\u7853 u ta; kh\'f4ng quen bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh, v\u7853 y n\'ean tha cho m\'ecnh m\u7897 t l\u7847 n?\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (s\'e1t th\uc0\u7909 c: kh\'f4ng t\u7915  th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u7875  gi\'e0nh l\u7907 i \'edch, l\u7915 a ti\u7873 n b\u7841 c c\u7911 a c\u7843 i c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n quen, h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \'edch ta, tranh th\u7911  s\u7921  t\'edn nhi\u7879 m c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i ta \u273 \u7875  l\u7915 a g\u7841 t h\u7885 )
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n lo l\u7855 ng nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i th\u7913  r\u432 \u7907 u h\u7895 n h\u7907 p n\'e0y c\u361 ng h\u417 i kh\'f3 x\u7917 , nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng kia l\u7841 i c\'f3 ph\u7847 n ngoan ngo\'e3n nghe l\u7901 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t. H\u7855 n th\u7847 m ngh\u297  ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7855 c t\u7897 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng n\'e0y r\u7891 i, hay l\'e0 c\'f3 nh\u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 r\u417 i v\'e0o tay \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o h\u7887 i ngay t\u7841 i ch\u7895 , th\u7917  kh\'e9o l\'e9o khuy\'ean nh\u7911  l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, d\u7913 t kho\'e1t kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a, c\u7921 c k\'ec c\'f3 nh\'e3n l\u7921 c m\'e0 v\'f9i \u273 \u7847 u bu\u7891 n b\u7921 c d\'f9ng b\u7919 a, gi\u7843  b\u7897  nh\u432  m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng t\u7891 n t\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t nhanh Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 say \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i ngay c\u7843  m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f3 x\u7917  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ch\'f3ng m\u7863 t h\u7891  \u273 \u7891 \'a0 m\u7863 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u432 a c\'e1i g\'ec c\u7853 u li\u7873 n u\u7889 ng c\'e1i \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh d\'f9 sao v\u7851 n c\'f2n m\u7845 y ph\u7847 n ngh\u297 a kh\'ed, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'f3i: "N\'e0y... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi? Tr\'ec Di\'ean say nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u417 i cong kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng: "Kh\'f4ng sao, bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, v\u7915 a v\u7863 n \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u ta v\u7873  ph\'f2ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ta d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng \u7903  c\'f9ng ch\u7895 , D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh g\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i n\u7919 a, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \'f4m vai Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7921 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean g\u7855 p m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng t\'f4m vi\'ean \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i b\'ean mi\u7879 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u258 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng s\u7869  kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Bi\uc0\u7871 t c\u7853 u ta s\u7869  kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u m\'e0 c\'f2n v\u7915 a \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t c\u7853 u ta u\u7889 ng nhi\u7873 u r\u432 \u7907 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y? D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh o\'e1n th\u7847 m trong b\u7909 ng, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\u7897 t m\'e0n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p l\u7855 m, ch\u7895  n\'e0o kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p l\u7841 i nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 say m\'ecnh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 no, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng quen bi\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7913  ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7871  n\'e0y nh\'ecn h\u7855 n gi\'fap Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u259 n s\u7869  r\u7845 t l\'fang t\'fang, D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh li\u7873 n \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "V\u7853 y, Di\u7879 p b\u7841 n h\u7885 c, bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u t\'f4i c\'f3 ch\'fat vi\u7879 c ph\u7843 i \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c. L\u7847 n sau c\'f3 c\u417  h\u7897 i l\u7841 i t\u7909  h\u7885 p."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7841 t \u273 \u432 a m\u7855 t nh\'ecn h\u7855 n r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, ch\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n khi b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t m\u7899 i c\'fai m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng, l\u7859 ng l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i trong tay \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m say \u273 \u7871 n m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng, mang ch\'fat ti\u7871 u \'fd nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n l\'ean b\u7901  m\'f4i mang theo m\'f9i r\u432 \u7907 u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u: "... Th\u7853 t kh\u7901 . Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i s\u7907  t\'f4i sao, th\u7871  n\'e0o l\u7841 i nghe l\u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y..."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh ngh\u297  m\'ecnh v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'f9 sao \u273 \'e3 quen nhau t\u7915  th\u7901 i \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c , h\'f4m nay l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7901 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u ta, nh\u432 ng say th\'e0nh d\u7841 ng \u273 \'f3 ch\u7855 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh ti\u7873 n n\u7893 i, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 i ra v\u7915 a mu\u7889 n thanh to\'e1n, nh\'e2n vi\'ean thu ng\'e2n l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i cho h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t: "Ti\'ean sinh, v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh t\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m thanh to\'e1n h\u7871 t r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh th\u7847 m ngh\u297  b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng n\'e0y c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'e1 c\'f3 ngh\u297 a kh\'ed, nh\u432 ng quay v\u7873  t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c l\u7841 i v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, h\u417 i kh\'f4ng y\'ean l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7889  \'fd g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n cho c\u7853 u, h\u7887 i c\u7853 u c\'f3 sao kh\'f4ng. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'fac n\'e0o \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7881 nh r\u432 \u7907 u tr\u7843  l\u7901 i tin nh\u7855 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
