\cf2 \cb3 T\uc0\u7841 i sao l\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'eam h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o, hai m\u7855 t nh\'ecn chung quanh m\u7897 t l\u432 \u7907 t xong x\u7889 c ch\u259 n l\'ean ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y b\'f2 xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 i m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n. Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 \u273 i \u273 \'e2u, l\'e0 \u273 i l\'fac n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\u7915 a b\'f2 xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c, c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n, ch\u7907 t nghe th\u7845 y "C\u7841 ch.." m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng c\u7917 a m\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\u432 \u7903 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7873 , nu\u7889 t ng\u7909 m n\u432 \u7899 c xu\u7889 ng h\'f4: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u v\u7873  r\u7891 i \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ng\uc0\u7921 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m nghi ng\u7901 , quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn, ch\'ednh di\u7879 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t tr\u7855 ng \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\'f3 m\uc0\u7897 t th\u7913  \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  c\u7917 a ra v\'e0o nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t xanh tr\u7855 ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 hai tay. D\u7901 i \'e1nh m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng... c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ch\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tim c\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i "B\u7897 p" m\u7897 t c\'e1i, qu\'ean m\u7845 t h\'f4 h\u7845 p, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i th\u7913  kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng, th\u7913  kia c\u361 ng nguy\'ean t\u7841 i ch\u7895  nh\'ecn c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'f4ng th\uc0\u7845 y n\'f3 gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t mi\u7879 ng, ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng "Eee...eeee " kh\'f4ng r\'f5\'97\'97gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\'edn hi\u7879 u radio c\u361  b\u7883  nhi\u7877 u s\'f3ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t gi\u7857 ng co nh\u432  v\u7853 y bao l\'e2u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7841 nh t\u7915 ng t\u7847 ng t\u7915 ng t\u7847 ng \u432 \u7899 t s\u361 ng n\u432 \u7899 c tr\'ean \'e1o ph\'f4ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. L\'fac v\u7915 a t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i c\u7853 u ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n qu\u7847 n \'e1o m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thay, ch\u7881  m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o ph\'f4ng r\u7897 ng th\'f9ng th\'ecnh, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7855 p ch\u259 n c\u7849 n th\u7853 n, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ngh\u297  c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\'fap c\u7853 u thay b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \u7847 y m\'f9i r\u432 \u7907 u kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7897 t nhi\'ean th\u7913  kia bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  c\u7917 a ra v\'e0o, v\u7867  m\u7863 t b\'ecnh \u7893 n nh\'ecn m\'ecnh: "Sao l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  c\u7917 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn h\uc0\u7855 n, m\'f4i m\u7845 p m\'e1y, \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t kh\u7843  n\u259 ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u. Tay tr\'e1i h\u7855 n v\u7855 t \'e1o kho\'e1c, nh\'ecn ra l\'e0 v\u7915 a t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i tr\u7903  v\u7873 , tay ph\u7843 i c\u7847 m theo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c t\'fai gi\u7845 y, h\u7855 n \u273 \u7863 t t\'fai gi\u7845 y l\'ean b\'e0n, l\u7845 y tay qu\u417  qu\u417  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "A Di\'ean, l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3, c\'f3..." m\uc0\u7897 t ch\u7919  "qu\u7927 " \u273 \'e8 tr\'ean l\u432 \u7905 i, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c phun kh\'f4ng ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 a tay b\u7855 t l\u7845 y c\'e1nh tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "... Sau khi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i t\'f4i \u273 \u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin nh\u7855 n n\'f3i l\u7841 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t, sau \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i l\u7841 i th\u7845 y... kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1nh tay, kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ch\'e2n..." C\u7853 u ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, trong c\u7863 p m\u7855 t tr\'e0n \u273 \u7847 y kinh ho\u7843 ng nghi ho\u7863 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'e9o c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng gh\u7871  tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n, im l\u7863 ng tr\u7845 n an v\u7895  vai c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7907 i m\u7897 t l\'e1t sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh m\u7899 i m\u7903  t\'fai gi\u7845 y, l\u7845 y c\u417 m h\u7897 p b\'ean trong ra. C\'f3 ch\'e1o h\u7843 i s\u7843 n, s\u7911 i c\u7843 o h\u7845 p, x\u432 \u417 ng s\u432 \u7901 n ninh, c\'e1nh g\'e0 lu\u7897 c, b\'e1nh bao kim sa v\'e0 m\u7897 t t\'fai h\u7841 ch \u273 \'e0o, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng m\'f3n \u259 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7845 t, gi\u7901  ph\'fat n\'e0y l\u7841 i c\'f3 v\u7867  \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t m\'ea ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\'e0 h\u7855 n c\u7889  \'fd mua t\u7915  m\u7897 t qu\'e1n r\u432 \u7907 u l\u7899 n n\u7893 i danh \u7903  g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7903  l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t t\u7915 ng h\u7897 p \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, m\'f9i th\u417 m v\'e0 h\u417 i n\'f3ng tho\'e1ng c\'e1i tr\'e0n ra, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \'f3i, \'e1nh m\u7855 t chuy\u7875 n \u273 \u7871 n th\u7913 c \u259 n tr\'ean b\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7891  \u259 n l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y an to\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7845 y \u273 \u361 a nh\'e9t v\'e0o trong tay c\u7853 u: "Mau \u259 n \u273 i, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u259 n xong r\u7891 i h\'e3y n\'f3i. Bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng \u259 n g\'ec, t\'f4i \u273 o\'e1n c\u7853 u t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i s\u7869  \u273 \'f3i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "... C\'e1m \uc0\u417 n." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  t\u7915  \u259 n, theo s\u7911 i c\u7843 o v\'e0o b\u7909 ng, m\u7897 t lu\u7891 ng \u7845 m \'e1p thu\u7897 c v\u7873  nh\'e2n gian c\u361 ng d\u7847 n d\u7847 n lan ra kh\u7855 p x\u432 \u417 ng c\u7889 t t\u7913  chi, l\'e0m \u7845 m th\'e2n th\u7875  b\u7883  s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m t\u7855 m, kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u kho\'e1c \'e1o t\u7855 m \u273 i ra, \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'f4m to\'e0n b\u7897  g\u7889 i \u273 \u7847 u ch\u259 n m\u7873 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u n\'e9m l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 ang \u259 n ch\'e1o, th\u7845 y th\u7871  m\u7903  to hai m\u7855 t, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng nu\u7889 t ch\'e1o trong mi\u7879 ng xu\u7889 ng h\'f4: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi... ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\'f3c v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u432 \u7899 t, ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 \u7915 ng c\'f3 v\u7897 i, t\u7915  t\u7915  \u259 n. T\u7889 i nay c\u7853 u c\u7913  ng\u7911  chung v\u7899 i t\'f4i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7919  kh\'ed c\u7911 a h\u7855 n r\u7845 t b\'ecnh th\u7843 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7863 t v\'e3nh, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n nguy\'ean nh\'e2n, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\u7871 t r\'f5 nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh b\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\u7841 ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7911  kinh h\'e3i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh n\'ean \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7899 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u432 a ra \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, l\u7841 i n\'f3i: "C\u7843 m \u417 n." \u272 \'e2y \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 l\u7847 n th\u7913  t\u432  c\u7853 u n\'f3i c\u7843 m \u417 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, tr\u7915  c\'e2u n\'e0y ra c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean n\'f3i g\'ec. Tuy r\u7857 ng g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i t\'e0 g\'ec, l\'fac n\'e0o c\u361 ng tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng t\u7889 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y qu\u7843  l\'e0 v\u7853 n may c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n c\'e1m \u417 n, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 vi\u7879 c t\'f4i n\'ean l\'e0m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i t\u7889 t \u273 \u7873 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, r\'f5 r\'e0ng chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n m\'ecnh v\u7851 n n\'f3i "\u272 \u7873 u l\'e0 vi\u7879 c t\'f4i n\'ean l\'e0m" . Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t m\u7863 t trong ng\u7921 c ngh\u297  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, m\u7897 t m\u7863 t c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\'e8o l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau h\uc0\u7871 t th\u7843 y v\'f4 s\u7921 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i b\'e1o c\'e1o c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c v\u7899 i th\u7847 y h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7847 y n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n n\'e0y th\u7847 y s\u7869  ph\u7843 i ra n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i tham gia m\u7845 y h\u7897 i ngh\u7883  h\u7885 c thu\u7853 t, \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i m\u7897 t th\'e1ng sau m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7903  v\u7873 , k\'eau c\u7853 u t\u7921  m\'ecnh c\u7889  g\u7855 ng cho t\u7889 t, c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec th\'ec vi\u7871 t mail li\'ean l\u7841 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi \uc0\u273 i ra t\u7915  v\u259 n ph\'f2ng th\u7847 y h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a ba, n\u7897 i dung cu\u7897 c g\u7885 i ph\'e1 v\u7905  m\u7897 t ng\'e0y t\'e2m t\'ecnh t\u7889 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Chung Vi\uc0\u7877 n tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean h\u7887 i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh h\u7885 c t\u7853 p sinh ho\u7841 t \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, sau \u273 \'f3 n\'f3i t\u7899 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c: "Con \'e0, ch\'fa \u272 \u7895  L\'e2m c\u7911 a con g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n t\u7899 i, n\'f3i con th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qua th\u259 m b\u7885 n h\u7885 , b\u7843 o con Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t qua \u259 n c\u417 m. N\u7871 u con kh\'f4ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\u7855 m, cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian th\'ec qua \u273 \'f3 m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, ch\u7847 n ch\u7915  m\u7897 t ch\'fat m\u7899 i n\'f3i, "Ba, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 con kh\'f4ng qua, th\u7847 y h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n k\'eau con l\'e0m c\'f9ng th\u7847 y m\u7897 t h\u7841 ng m\u7909 c, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  v\u7915 a m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u l\'e0m, c\u7843  nh\'f3m m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u t\u259 ng ca, Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ngh\u7881 . T\u7899 i ch\u7895  ch\'fa s\u7869  ph\u7843 i \u273 i h\u417 n m\u7897 t gi\u7901 , d\'f9 ch\u7881  \u259 n b\u7919 a c\u417 m c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i h\u7871 t n\u7917 a ng\'e0y, l\'fac n\'e0y xin ngh\u7881  kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p l\u7855 m, \u273 \u7875  con g\u7885 i cho ch\'fa, \u273 \u7907 i khi n\'e0o c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian s\u7869  \u273 i th\u259 m..."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 ang n\'f3i d\u7889 i, th\u7847 y h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n n\'e0y s\u7869  ra n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i d\u7921  h\u7897 i ngh\u7883 , th\u7843  c\u7853 u m\u7897 t th\'e1ng r\u7843 nh r\u7895 i li\'ean t\u7909 c, n\'e0o c\'f3 h\u7841 ng m\u7909 c t\u259 ng ca g\'ec. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i qua loa v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  h\u7879  tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng d\'f9 sao v\u7851 n l\u7845 y vi\u7879 c h\u7885 c l\'e0m tr\u7885 ng, nghe c\u7853 u n\'f3i th\u7871  Tr\'ec Chung Vi\u7877 n qu\u7843  nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng b\u7843 o c\u7853 u \u273 i n\u7919 a, ch\u7881  d\u7863 n d\'f2: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, v\u7853 y con nh\u7899  g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho ch\'fa, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7845 t nh\u7899  con. H\u7871 t b\u7853 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec th\'ec mua ch\'fat qu\'e0 cho b\'e0 tr\u7867  v\u7899 i ch\'fa th\'edm, \u273 i th\u259 m b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7897 t ch\'fat..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean "V\'e2ng v\'e2ng" \uc0\u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng li\'ean t\u7909 c c\u7843  bu\u7893 i m\u7899 i c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa \uc0\u272 \u7895  L\'e2m m\'e0 ba nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i l\'e0 con trai c\u7911 a b\'e0 tr\u7867 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 tr\uc0\u7867  l\'e0 em g\'e1i ru\u7897 t c\u7911 a b\'e0 n\u7897 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, theo l\u7901 i ba n\'f3i l\'fac nh\u7887  ba v\'e0 ch\'fa v\u7851 n th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean c\'f9ng nhau ch\u417 i, quan h\u7879  r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, cho \u273 \u7871 n khi ba l\'ean c\u7845 p ba, b\u7903 i v\'ec ch\u7891 ng c\u7911 a b\'e0 tr\u7867  thay \u273 \u7893 i c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c n\'ean c\u7843  nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7899 i chuy\u7875 n \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A. Nh\u432 ng d\'f9 v\u7853 y hai nh\'e0 v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\u7855 t \u273 \u7913 t li\'ean h\u7879 , ng\'e0y l\u7877  ng\'e0y t\u7871 t v\u7851 n th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \'e2n c\u7847 n h\u7887 i th\u259 m nhau, l\'fac ch\'fa \u272 \u7895  L\'e2m quay v\u7873  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  H c\u361 ng s\u7869  qua th\u259 m nh\'e0 c\u7853 u, khi c\'f2n b\'e9 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n hay g\u7863 p ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fa n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean thi \u273 \u7853 u \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c A, ba m\u7865  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t vui m\u7915 ng, ngh\u7881  h\'e8 n\u259 m l\u7899 p m\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n v\'f9ng l\'e2n c\u7853 n ch\u417 i s\u7899 m m\u7897 t ch\'fat, thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n \u273 i th\u259 m nh\'e0 ch\'fa. Khi \u273 \'f3 ch\u7891 ng b\'e0 tr\u7867  \u273 \'e3 qua \u273 \u7901 i, ch\'fa l\'e0 con m\u7897 t, trong nh\'e0 c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f2n b\'e0 tr\u7867 , ch\'fa, th\'edm v\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a con trai c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7915 a m\u7899 i l\'ean n\u259 m nh\u7845 t \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, m\u7897 t nh\'e0 b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  trong m\u7897 t c\u259 n nh\'e0 ba t\u7847 ng trong khu bi\u7879 t th\u7921  nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 n nh\'e0 n\'e0y c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 t\u7915  kh\'e1 l\'e2u, h\u417 n hai m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7891 ng c\u7911 a b\'e0 tr\u7867  nh\u7901  ch\'fat quan h\u7879  mua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ki\u7871 n tr\'fac k\u7871 t c\u7845 u kh\'f4ng gian \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ki\u7875 u t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i c\u361 , t\u7915  r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 i\u7875 m c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra nh\'e0 \u273 \'e3 nhi\u7873 u tu\u7893 i, \u273 i\u7873 u t\u7889 t l\'e0 kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch gi\u7919 a c\'e1c nh\'e0 \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t l\u7899 n, kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng khu bi\u7879 t th\u7921  b\'e2y gi\u7901  nh\'e0 \u7903  t\u7853 p trung san s\'e1t , b\u7903 i v\u7853 y c\u361 ng r\u7845 t y\'ean t\u297 nh, c\'f3 ch\'fat m\'f9i v\u7883  t\'e1ch bi\u7879 t th\u7871  gian.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi th\uc0\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n ch\'fa v\'e0 b\'e0 tr\u7867  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t vui m\u7915 ng, nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh chi\'eau \u273 \'e3i b\u7885 n h\u7885 . K\u7871 t qu\u7843  bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i l\'fac \u259 n c\u417 m Tr\'ec Chung Vi\u7877 n nh\u7853 n \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i n\'f3i c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c x\u7843 y ra ch\'fat v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , \'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c tr\u7903  l\u7841 i x\u7917  l\'fd. Tr\'ec Chung Vi\u7877 n v\u7889 n \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f9ng v\u7907  mang con trai \u273 i ch\u417 i \u7903  v\'f9ng ph\u7909  c\u7853 n, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac nh\u7853 p h\u7885 c th\'ec s\u7869  th\'f4ng b\'e1o cho ch\'fa, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i vi\u7879 c n\'e0y l\'e0m r\u7889 i to\'e0n b\u7897  k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 \'f3 Ch\'fa \u272 \u7895  L\'e2m li\u7873 n ng\u7887  l\u7901 i n\'f3i c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c anh c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n th\'ec c\u7913  \u273 \u432 a ch\u7883  d\'e2u v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i, \u273 \u7875  Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean \u7903  l\u7841 i ch\u7895  em, d\'f9 sao ph\'f2ng tr\u7889 ng c\'f2n r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, c\u361 ng v\u7915 a v\u7863 n \u273 \u7875  Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean d\u7841 y h\u7885 c cho em h\u7885 . \u272 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi khai gi\u7843 ng em s\u7869  \u273 \u432 a th\u7857 ng b\'e9 \u273 i, Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 thanh ni\'ean tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh, c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  ch\u259 m s\'f3c b\u7843 n th\'e2n r\u7891 i, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng b\u7899 t ph\u7843 i \u273 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\'e2m t\'e2m ni\u7879 m ni\u7879 m mu\u7889 n \u273 i xem tri\u7875 n l\'e3m khoa h\u7885 c k\u7929  thu\u7853 t h\'e0ng kh\'f4ng c\u7911 a th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A, tri\u7875 n l\'e3m n\'e0y ng\'e0y mai s\u7869  k\u7871 t th\'fac, cho n\'ean c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t th\u7901 i bi\u7871 t th\u7871  m\'e0 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng \u7903  l\u7841 i nh\'e0 ch\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e0 n\'e0y n\'f3i l\'e0 c\'f3 ba l\uc0\u7847 u, nh\u432 ng k\u7923  th\u7853 t l\u7847 u ba di\u7879 n t\'edch r\u7845 t nh\u7887 , m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng nh\u7887  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'f9ng l\'e0m ph\'f2ng ch\u7913 a \u273 \u7891 , m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng c\'f3 c\u7917 a s\u7893  d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m ph\'f2ng cho kh\'e1ch, c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng \u7903  gi\u7919 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e0 tr\u7867  t\'edn Ph\u7853 t b\u7889  tr\'ed th\'e0nh Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng. B\'ean trong Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t b\'e0n th\u7901  Ph\u7853 t \u7903  ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a, b\'ean trong th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng Ph\u7853 t T\u7893  B\u244 \u768  T\'e1t, c\u361 ng b\'e0y l\u432  h\u432 \u417 ng, hoa qu\u7843  v\'e0 b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t. Tr\'ean b\u7889 n b\u7913 c t\u432 \u7901 ng treo tranh v\u7869  c\'f5i T\'e2y Ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u7921 c l\u7841 c, V\'e2n H\u7843 i ch\'fang Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u7891 , H\'e0n S\u417 n h\u7887 i Th\u7853 p \u272 \u7855 c, v\'e2n v\'e2n. 
\f2\i (\uc0\u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n Ph\u7853 t gi\'e1o)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa th\'edm, b\'e0 tr\uc0\u7867  v\'e0 em h\u7885  m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng, \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  l\u7847 u hai, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  ph\'f2ng cho kh\'e1ch l\u7847 u ba n\'e0y. M\u7897 t m\'ecnh m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng l\u7847 u, di\u7879 n t\'edch c\u259 n ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7887 , c\'f3 gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n, c\'f3 ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m v\'e0 s\'e2n th\u432 \u7907 ng, c\u7853 u c\'f2n r\u7845 t vui v\u7867 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u v\u7915 a thi \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c xong, c\'f2n v\'e0i ng\'e0y n\u7919 a m\u7899 i khai gi\u7843 ng, qu\u7843  \u273 \'fang l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m v\'f4 \u432 u v\'f4 lo nh\u7845 t. T\u7889 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean ba m\u7865  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7901 i \u273 i, m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u7853 u ng\u7911  \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\'fa v\u7851 n r\u7845 t ngon, ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau c\'f9ng em h\u7885  \u273 i xem tri\u7875 n l\'e3m, l\u7841 i \u273 i ch\u417 i c\u7843  bu\u7893 i, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  c\u417 m t\u7889 i m\u7899 i tr\u7903  v\u7873 , \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t vui v\u7867 . L\'fac \u7845 y em h\u7885  c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881  h\'e8 v\u7851 n ch\u432 a khai gi\u7843 ng, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7845 t h\u7907 p nhau, \u259 n t\u7889 i xong Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 em h\u7885  l\u7841 i c\'f9ng nhau ch\u417 i game \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901 , ch\u417 i m\u7897 t ng\'e0y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 m\u7879 t m\u7887 i, t\u7855 m r\u7917 a xong v\u7915 a d\'ednh g\u7889 i \u273 \u7847 u li\u7873 n ng\u7911 . C\u7853 u ng\u7911  r\u7845 t s\'e2u, d\'f9 c\'f3 t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng g\'ec kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau l\'fac t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a ba, ba d\u7863 n d\'f2 c\u7853 u \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\'fa ph\u7843 i hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n. C\u7853 u li\u7873 n th\'e0nh th\'e0nh th\u7853 t th\u7853 t \u7903  nh\'e0 c\u7843  ng\'e0y, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m d\u7853 y \u273 i Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng ni\u7879 m kinh Ph\u7853 t cho b\'e0 tr\u7867  m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a gi\'fap em h\u7885  l\'e0m v\u7857 n th\u7855 n, bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u th\'ec d\u7841 y h\u7885 c cho em h\u7885 , c\u417 m n\u432 \u7899 c xong xu\'f4i l\u7841 i c\'f9ng em h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  g\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e1nh c\u7847 u l\'f4ng, g\u7847 n m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  m\u7899 i v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\u7853 u ng\u7911  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, ng\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 i\u7873 u h\'f2a \u273 \'e3 ng\u7915 ng ch\u7841 y, kh\'f4ng kh\'ed trong ph\'f2ng n\'f3ng rang, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng. Trong kh\'f4ng kh\'ed n\'f3ng b\u7913 c \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7913  h\u417 i l\u7841 nh t\u7915  ph\'eda sau g\u7855 t gao bao l\u7845 y m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
