\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn ra sau, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y ai, nh\u432 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o v\u7915 a r\u7891 i r\u7845 t th\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  nh\u7887  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ti\u7871 p thu gi\'e1o d\u7909 c ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a duy v\u7853 t, lu\'f4n lu\'f4n coi chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927  l\'e0 tr\'f2 l\u7915 a g\u7841 t v\'f4 c\u259 n c\u7913 , \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ngh\u297  theo chi\u7873 u h\u432 \u7899 ng ma qu\u7927  l\'e0m lo\u7841 n, ch\u7881  coi m\'ecnh l\'e0 ng\u7911  l\u417  m\u417  sinh \u7843 o gi\'e1c, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 \u273 em gi\u7845 c m\u417  v\u7899 i th\u7921 c t\u7871  nh\u7853 p l\'e0m m\u7897 t. C\u7853 u n\'f3ng \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y s\u7901  \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n m\u7903  \u273 i\u7873 u h\'f2a l\'ean r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ng\u7911  say. Trong l\'fac ng\u7911  m\u417  t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \'f4m m\'ecnh vu\u7889 t ve m\'ecnh, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u7881  cho l\'e0 m\u7897 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n l\u432 u t\'e2m, v\u7851 n ng\u7911  say s\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau b\'e0 tr\uc0\u7867  l\u7841 i t\u7899 i t\'ecm c\u7853 u \u273 \u7885 c kinh s\'e1ch cho m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng ch\'fa th\'edm b\u7873  b\u7897 n nhi\u7873 u vi\u7879 c, em h\u7885  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c "Phong ki\u7871 n m\'ea t\'edn" c\u7911 a b\'e0 m\'ecnh th\'ec l\u7841 i x\'ec m\u361 i coi th\u432 \u7901 ng, b\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0 c\u361 ng r\u7845 t c\'f4 qu\u7841 nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng tin c\'e1c lo\u7841 i t\'f4n gi\'e1o, nh\u432 ng ch\'fat vi\u7879 c nh\u7887  n\'e0y c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0, coi nh\u432  l\'e0 gi\'fap b\'e0 \u273 \u7905  bu\u7891 n. B\'e0 tr\u7867  hi\u7871 m khi g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t h\u7853 u b\u7889 i ki\'ean nh\u7851 n s\u7861 n l\'f2ng gi\'fap m\'ecnh n\'ean r\u7845 t vui v\u7867 , s\'e1ng s\u7899 m ng\u7911  d\u7853 y li\u7873 n nh\u7899  \u273 i t\'ecm Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 h\u7887 i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean \'e0, h\'f4m nay con l\u7841 i gi\'fap b\'e0 \u273 \u7885 c kinh s\'e1ch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1p v\'e2ng, \u259 n s\'e1ng xong li\u7873 n theo b\'e0 l\'ean Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng tr\'ean l\u7847 u ba. B\'ean tr\'e1i Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\'e1i s\u7853 p r\u7897 ng b\u7857 ng m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7853 u v\u7899 i b\'e0 m\u7863 t \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t ng\u7891 i \u7903  ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3, c\u7853 u c\u7847 m l\u7845 y m\u7897 t quy\u7875 n kinh Ph\'e2\u803 t ni\u7879 m cho b\'e0, b\'e0 h\'edp m\u7855 t c\u432 \u7901 i nghe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i tr\u432 a \u259 n c\u417 m bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u c\'f9ng em h\u7885  \u273 i ch\u417 i b\'f3ng r\u7893 , m\u7897 t ng\'e0y l\u7841 i tr\'f4i qua nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \'eam khuya l\'fac ng\u7911 , ng\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng kh\'ed xung quanh oi b\u7913 c d\'ednh d\u7899 p, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 \'f4m eo m\'ecnh, nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  l\u7841 nh h\u417 n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7883  h\u7855 n \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c th\u7853 t ra r\u7845 t tho\u7843 i m\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Li\'ean t\uc0\u7909 c hai ng\'e0y m\u417  c\'f9ng gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng n\'e0y qu\u7843  th\u7921 c h\u7871 t s\u7913 c ch\'e2n th\u7853 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 tr\'ec \u273 \u7897 n \u273 i ch\u259 ng n\u7919 a c\u361 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng. C\u7853 u t\u7915  trong gi\u7845 c ng\u7911  say ki\'ean c\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn nh\'ecn, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai. L\u7841 i l\u7847 n t\'ecm \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'ean g\u7889 i m\u7903  l\'ean xem, th\u7901 i gian l\'e0 ba gi\u7901  s\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7911 , li\'ean t\u7909 c d\'f9ng m\'f3ng tay b\u7845 m v\'e0o l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c h\u417 i \u273 au khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u duy tr\'ec thanh t\u7881 nh. Qua ch\u7915 ng h\u417 n m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891 , c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" kia m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a \'f4m eo c\u7853 u, th\u7853 m ch\'ed h\u7841  n\u7909  h\'f4n l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o l\'ean ph\u7847 n g\'e1y l\u7897  ra c\u7911 a c\u7853 u... C\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\u7909  h\'f4n kia qu\'e1 r\'f5 r\'e0ng, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n li\u7871 m l\'e1p nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng m\'fat v\'e0o...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o t\uc0\u7921  an \u7911 i m\'ecnh \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\u7897 ng n\u7919 a, c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c m\u7903  to m\u7855 t ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, qu\'e9t m\u7855 t kh\u7855 p c\u259 n ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, v\u7863 n m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n gi\u432 \u7901 ng. \u272 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7853 u ki\u7875 m tra c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\'f9ng v\u7899 i c\u7917 a th\u7911 y tinh n\u7889 i ti\u7871 p ban c\'f4ng b\'ean ngo\'e0i\'97\'97hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a th\'f4ng v\'e0o ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f3a t\u7915  trong r\u7845 t c\u7849 n th\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i s\u7907 , kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ng\u7911  ti\u7871 p, sau khi tr\u7903  l\u7841 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng li\u7873 n b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n ng\u7891 i ch\u417 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n n\u259 m gi\u7901  s\'e1ng, \u273 \u7871 n khi th\u7845 y b\u7847 u tr\u7901 i ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  l\u7901  m\u7901  n\u7893 i l\'ean m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng b\u7841 c m\u7899 i n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng l\u7841 i. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0 ng\u7911  \'edt, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  d\u7853 y s\u7899 m, m\u7897 t gi\u7901  n\u7919 a b\'e0 tr\u7867  s\u7869  r\u7901 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng s\'e1t v\'e1ch b\'e1i Ph\u7853 t. \'dd ngh\u297  n\'e0y l\'e0m c\u7853 u tho\'e1ng an t\'e2m, tr\'f9m ch\u259 n l\u7841 i ng\u7911  th\u7853 t say.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n tr\u7843 i qua l\'fac n\'e3y n\'f3i cho c\'f9ng c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f9ng lo\u7841 i v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n "Qu\u7927  \'e1p gi\u432 \u7901 ng" d\'e2n gian l\u432 u truy\u7873 n, m\u7863 c d\'f9 c\'f3 ch\'fat qu\u7927  d\u7883 , nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ch\u432 a khi\u7871 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 t s\u7921  khi\u7871 p s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i g\uc0\u7885 i l\'e0 "M\u7897 t n\u259 m b\u7883  r\u7855 n c\u7855 n m\u432 \u7901 i n\u259 m s\u7907  d\'e2y th\u7915 ng", t\u7915  nh\u7887  Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927 , t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u432 \u417 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng b\u7883  r\u7855 n c\u7855 n, t\u7915  nh\u7887  l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ba d\u7841 y nam t\u7917  h\'e1n \u273 \u7841 i tr\u432 \u7907 ng phu ph\u7843 i d\u361 ng c\u7843 m, hai \u273 \'eam qua gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7847 n h\u7891 n n\'e1t th\u7847 n t\'ednh, v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \u273 \u7911  \u273 \u7875  khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u b\u7895 ng ch\u7889 c b\u7883  d\u7885 a \u273 \u7871 n r\'e1ch gan.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'eam ng\'e0y th\u7913  t\u432  Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ng\u7911  hay ki\u7871 m c\u7899  k\'eau em h\u7885  b\u7847 u b\u7841 n v\u7899 i m\'ecnh. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u t\'e2m tr\'ed ngh\u297  nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m ni\u7879 m kinh Ph\'e2\u803 t cho b\'e0 tr\u7867  xong li\u7873 n m\u432 \u7907 n cu\u7889 n kinh Ph\'e2\u803 t \u7903  \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7875  d\u432 \u7899 i g\u7889 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i l\'fac ng\u7911  c\u7889  \'fd kh\'f4ng c\u7903 i qu\u7847 n ngo\'e0i v\u7899 i \'e1o s\u417 mi tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7913  m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\'e0 ng\u7911 . M\'f9a h\'e8 qu\u7847 n \'e1o m\u7887 ng, c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7847 u trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n, li\'ean t\u7909 c n\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea kh\'f4ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n ng\u7911 , ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7901 i gian tr\'f4i qua r\u7845 t l\'e2u, trong ph\'f2ng y\'ean t\u297 nh, t\u7845 t c\u7843  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  d\u7847 n d\u7847 n d\'e2ng l\'ean, \'fd th\u7913 c c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i n\u7919 a, r\u7845 t t\u7921  nhi\'ean li\u7873 n ng\u7911 ...\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7917 a \u273 \'eam m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng ch\u7907 t c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay \u273 ang m\u7903  c\'fac \'e1o s\u417  mi c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 a tay l\'ean g\u7841 t c\'e1i tay kia ra, nh\u432 ng c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7841 m th\u7845 y, ch\u7881  \u273 \u7909 ng t\u7899 i ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c t\u7881 nh t\'e1o l\u7841 i, ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y \u7845 n m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn, \'e1o s\u417  mi ng\u7855 n tay m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  c\u7903 i ba chi\u7871 c c\'fac ph\'eda tr\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7849 n th\u7853 n l\u7845 y kinh Ph\'e2\u803 t d\u432 \u7899 i g\u7889 i ra \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, m\u432 \u7907 n \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0u cam c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 b\u7889 n ph\'eda.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7845 y th\u7913  v\u7853 t d\u7909 ng ban ng\'e0y c\u7853 u th\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e8n gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\'f3e l\'ean v\'e0i c\'e1i, l\u7841 i "Ph\u7909 t" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng d\u7853 p t\u7855 t, trong ph\'f2ng tho\'e1ng c\'e1i l\'e2m v\'e0o trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843  kinh, kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 o\u7841 t kinh Ph\'e2\u803 t trong tay c\u7853 u, tay c\u7853 u c\u7847 m kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c, kinh Ph\'e2\u803 t "B\u7897 p" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p xu\u7889 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo \uc0\u273 \'f3 mu\u7889 n xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7863 t, c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p \u273 \u432 a tay li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \'f4m eo m\'ecnh t\'fam m\'ecnh l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  mu\u7889 n \'e1p c\u7853 u l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ho\uc0\u7843 ng s\u7907 , tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  n\'e0y d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e8 n\'e9n l\'e2u r\u7891 i, ngh\u7865 n qu\'e1 m\u7913 c, h\'f4m nay hung h\u259 ng h\u417 n r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i hai ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean linh quang ch\u7907 t l\'f3e, gi\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p \u273 i, sau khi ra s\u7913 c gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a li\u7873 n k\'e9o c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  ch\u7841 y ra ngo\'e0i h\'e0nh lang, ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a chui v\'e0o, l\u7841 i \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i th\u7853 t ch\u7863 t kh\'f3a tr\'e1i b\'ean trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t h\u417 i l\'e0m xong t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\u7853 u m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 a l\u432 ng ch\u7855 n c\u7917 a, th\u7903  ph\'ec ph\'f2, c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tim m\'ecnh \u273 \u7853 p k\u7883 ch li\u7879 t, l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t to\'e0n m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7841 nh. \'c1nh \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng y\u7871 u \u7899 t t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  chi\u7871 u v\'e0o, m\u417  m\u417  h\u7891  h\u7891  chi\u7871 u ra c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng l\u7901  m\u7901  b\'ean trong Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ngh\u297  y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i h\u7859 n l\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 n v\'e0o trong Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tho\'e1ng b\'ecnh t\uc0\u297 nh m\u7897 t ch\'fat, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7847 n m\'f2 v\u432 \u417 n tay \u273 \u7883 nh m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n ph\'f2ng, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng s\u7901  th\u7845 y c\'f4ng t\u7855 c, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i s\u7901  th\u7845 y m\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" l\u7841 nh ng\u7855 t \'97\'97 th\u7913  kia \u273 ang \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7913 ng bao l\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i ng\'e2y ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7845 y l\u7841 i tinh th\u7847 n quay ng\u432 \u7901 i mu\u7889 n m\u7903  c\u7917 a. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7917 a Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i b\u7883  c\u7853 u kh\'f3a c\u7913 ng, l\'fac n\'e0y b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7903  ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u xoay kh\'f3a li\'ean t\u7909 c m\u7897 t ph\'fat \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891 , cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  tuy\u7879 t v\u7885 ng t\u7915  b\u7887 , run r\u7849 y t\u7915 ng ch\'fat m\u7897 t lui v\u7873  ph\'eda sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\'e8o v\u7901 n chu\u7897 t t\u7915 ng ch\'fat m\u7897 t t\u7899 i g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7853 m ch\u7841 p l\'f9i l\u7841 i, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3, c\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn, b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7909 ng \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7887 , kh\'f4ng th\u7875  lui \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7907  h\'e3i tuy\u7879 t v\u7885 ng khi \u273 \'f3 th\u7853 t kh\'f3 m\'e0 n\'f3i th\'e0nh l\u7901 i, c\u7853 u s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e2m thanh n\'e0o, ch\'e2n m\u7873 m nh\u361 n l\'f9i l\u7841 i ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, tr\u7885 ng t\'e2m b\u7845 t \u7893 n, ng\'e3 ng\u7917 a xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia t\u7915  ch\'ednh di\u7879 n \'e1p xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong Ph\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng t\u7889 i om, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  kia \'e1p \u7903  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh, c\u7903 i t\u7915 ng chi\u7871 c c\'fac \'e1o c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra... B\'e0n tay h\u417 i l\u7841 nh g\u7841 t v\u7841 t \'e1o tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u sang hai b\'ean, xoa ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  k\'edch th\'edch s\u7907  run c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i, n\u7913 c n\u7903  kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thanh \'e2m n\'e0o, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng r\'ean r\u7881  th\u7853 t nh\u7887  kh\'f4ng th\'e0nh l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
