\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, nh\u7863 t qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7863 c v\'e0o, v\u7851 n s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n run r\u7849 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd ngh\uc0\u297  \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 b\'e0 tr\u7867  ch\u7855 c s\u7855 p \u273 i b\'e1i Ph\u7853 t, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  b\u7883  b\'e0 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean \u273 i t\u7899 i b\'ean c\u7917 a, c\'e1nh c\u7917 a \u273 \'eam qua b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7903  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\'fac n\'e0y ch\u7881  c\u7847 n v\u7863 n kh\'f3a \u273 \u7849 y nh\u7865  m\u7897 t c\'e1i li\u7873 n m\u7903  ra. C\u7853 u l\u7863 ng l\u7869  tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh, \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c g\u432 \u417 ng\'97\'97 tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7845 u v\u7871 t g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3. M\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \'eam qua gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u7881  l\'e0 ch\'ednh m\'ecnh m\u417  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng.\cb1 \
