\cb3 Hai m\uc0\u7855 t s\u432 ng \u273 \u7887  nh\u432  th\u7887  kia kh\'f4ng l\u7915 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\'e0 tr\u7867  k\'e9o c\u7853 u h\'edp m\u7855 t nh\'ecn h\u7891 i l\'e2u, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 au l\'f2ng d\u7863 n d\'f2 c\u7853 u ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i cho t\u7889 t.\cb1 \
