\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t n\'ean n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7843  nh\'e0 ch\'fa chuy\u7879 n ph\'e1t sinh h\'f4m qua nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, do d\u7921  h\u7891 i l\'e2u cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n n\'edn thinh b\u7887  qua kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i \'97\'97 c\u7843  nh\'e0 ch\'fa c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, tin l\u7901 i m\'ecnh hay kh\'f4ng t\u7841 m th\u7901 i kh\'f3 n\'f3i, d\'f9 c\'f3 tin t\u432 \u7903 ng chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927  qu\u7845 y ph\'e1 n\'e0y th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. B\'e2y gi\u7901  xem ra th\u7913  kia c\u361 ng ch\u7881  qu\u7845 n l\'ean m\'ecnh, c\'f3 v\u7867  nh\u432  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng l\'e0m h\u7841 i nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c trong nh\'e0 n\'e0y, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ch\'ednh x\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0 m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7885 c ph\u7843 i ch\u7895  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
