\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u7903  to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \'e8n tr\u7847 n v\'e0 \u273 \'e8n gi\u432 \u7901 ng trong ph\'f2ng l\'ean, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u361 ng s\u7841 c pin \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, ng\u7891 i \u7903  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7903  game chi\u7871 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng hay ch\u417 i\'97\'97 tr\'f2 ch\u417 i th\'f4ng b\'e1o hi\u7879 n \u273 ang c\'f3 n\u259 m m\u432 \u417 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang tham gia \u273 \u7841 i chi\u7871 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng, ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n trong m\'e0n h\'ecnh c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng m\'ecnh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y an t\'e2m h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng d\'f9 sao \u273 \'eam qua Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng b\u7883  gi\'e0y v\'f2 \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i ch\u432 a ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y gi\u7901 , kh\'f3 tr\'e1nh kh\u7887 i s\u7913 c l\u7921 c tinh th\u7847 n k\'e9m, l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u v\u7851 n c\'f2n ng\u7891 i ch\u417 i, v\u7873  sau bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh d\u7921 a ch\u417 i, \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh n\u7857 m ch\u417 i... Ch\u417 i m\u7897 t l\'fac, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 ang s\'e1ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  c\u7853 u v\u7913 t sang m\u7897 t b\'ean, m\'e0 ch\u7911  nh\'e2n th\'ec \u273 \'e3 h\u417 i nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i an \u7893 n ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t ng\u7911  bao l\'e2u, \'fd th\u7913 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i thanh t\u7881 nh, trong m\u7883 t m\u7901  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'e8n ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  t\u7855 t t\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o, xung quanh t\u7889 i om, m\'e0 th\u7913  kia l\u7841 i \u273 ang m\u7863 t \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t \'f4m l\u7845 y m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng co r\'fam l\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7841 y. C\u7853 u qu\'e1 bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 , c\u7843 nh trong m\u417  t\u7889 i tr\u7847 m mang theo m\'f3c c\'e2u li\'ean t\u7909 c l\'f4i k\'e9o c\u7853 u n\u7863 ng n\u7873  ch\'ecm xu\u7889 ng, khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7885  ngu\u7853 y n\u7893 i... Trong b\'f3ng \u273 \'eam c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, b\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u7841 y kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t, ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2u c\u361 ng nh\u432  nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 th\uc0\u7913  kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 n th\'eam b\u432 \u7899 c n\'e0o, ch\u7881  \'f4m l\u7845 y c\u7853 u, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng h\u7841  xu\u7889 ng m\u7897 t hai c\'e1i h\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'e0i ph\uc0\u7847 n \'fd th\u7913 c thanh t\u7881 nh kia c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7845 t kinh ho\u7843 ng, th\'e2n th\u7875  r\u7891 i l\u7841 i qu\'e1 y\u7871 u nh\u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng xu\u7845 t ra n\u7893 i m\u7897 t tia kh\'ed l\u7921 c. C\u7921 c k\u7923  m\'e2u thu\u7851 n l\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7853 y m\'e0 \u7903  trong n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i n\'e0y, \u7903  trong l\u7891 ng ng\u7921 c c\u7911 a th\u7913  n\'e0y l\u7841 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n an \u7893 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ng\u7911  \'97\'97 say gi\u7845 c v\'f4 m\u7897 ng, th\u7859 ng cho \u273 \u7871 n h\'f4m sau tr\u7901 i s\'e1ng r\u7905 , em h\u7885  l\'ean l\u7847 u g\'f5 c\u7917 a g\u7885 i c\u7917 a m\u7899 i d\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  \u273 \'f3 v\u7873  sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ch\'fa n\u7919 a, nh\u432 ng k\'fd \u7913 c v\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 lu\'f4n qu\u7849 n quanh trong \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng xua \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7907  chuy\u7879 n ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ch\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 May m\'e0 b\uc0\u7889 n n\u259 m \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh an v\'f4 s\u7921 , b\u7845 y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u m\u7899 i l\u7841 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n ki\'ean \u273 \u7883 nh tin t\u432 \u7903 ng ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a duy v\u7853 t, trong ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c an \u7911 i \'e1m th\u7883  b\u7843 n th\'e2n r\u7857 ng chuy\u7879 n kia ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng xu\'e2n mang s\u7855 c th\'e1i kinh d\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7847 n d\'e0, ch\'ednh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nh\u7899  r\'f5 m\u7845 y \u273 \'eam qu\u7927  d\u7883  \u273 \'e3 tr\u7843 i qua \u273 \'f3 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  ph\'e1t sinh hay ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u417 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng \u273 ang l\'fac c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p l\'e3ng qu\'ean chuy\u7879 n m\'f9a h\'e8 n\u259 m \u273 \'f3, h\'f4m nay c\u7853 u l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i ch\'fang \'97\'97 l\'fac \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\'fa ch\u7881  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  kia kh\'f4ng ki\'eang n\u7875  mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec th\'ec l\'e0m \u7913 c hi\u7871 p m\'ecnh, \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c n\'e0y th\u7871  nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e3 hai l\u7847 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\u7841 ng \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  c\u7911 a ch\'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7841 i th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c m\u7845 u ch\u7889 t n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 i th\u259 m nh\'e0 ch\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i sau khi tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi chuy\u7879 n th\u7847 y h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ph\u7843 i ra n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i tham gia h\u7897 i ngh\u7883  h\u7885 c thu\u7853 t, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i r\u7845 t nghe v\'e0o l\'f2ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, nh\'ecn nh\u432  r\u7845 t b\'ecnh th\u7843 n \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883 : "N\u7871 u s\u7855 p t\u7899 i th\u7847 y c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y th\'ec h\u7859 n l\'e0 c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\'ecm c\u7853 u, d\u7841 o n\'e0y c\u7853 u n\'f3i hay tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7845 y th\u7913  kia ch\u7855 c l\'e0 v\'ec nghe m\u7845 y tin t\u7913 c hung \'e1n g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y r\u7891 i v\'f4 th\u7913 c t\u7921  \'e1m th\u7883  t\'e2m l\'fd sinh \u7843 o gi\'e1c. C\u7853 u c\'f3 mu\u7889 n c\'f9ng t\'f4i v\u7873  nh\'e0 t\'f4i \u7903  hai ng\'e0y kh\'f4ng? Thay \u273 \u7893 i m\'f4i tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 khi s\u7869  kh\'e1 h\u417 n \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\uc0\u297  ngh\u297 , c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng n\'f3i r\u7845 t c\'f3 l\'fd, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n do d\u7921  ch\u432 a d\'e1m quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh: "Li\u7879 u c\'f3 l\'e0m phi\u7873 n ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng?" M\u7863 c d\'f9 l\'e0 b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng, nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao b\u7885 n h\u7885  quen bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a t\u7899 i n\u7917 a n\u259 m, t\'f9y ti\u7879 n \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta \u7903  nh\u7901  v\u7851 n r\u7845 t ng\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4n h\'f2a n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng sao \u273 \'e2u, d\'f9 sao trong nh\'e0 c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\'ecnh t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean "H\uc0\u7843 " m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "V\u7853 y nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u273 \'e2u? Kh\'f4ng \u7903  nh\'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7865  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "... \u7914 , b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u7903  n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u h\'e0nh tr\'ecnh \u273 i nh\'e0 h\u7855 n. Ng\u7891 i trong xe Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'e0ng \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c xe ch\u7841 y c\'e0ng nhanh, c\'e0ng \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c xung quanh l\u7841 i c\'e0ng tr\u7903  n\'ean quen thu\u7897 c, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7889 t l\'ean: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\'e0 c\u7853 u \u7903  ph\'eda n\'e0y \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \'e1p: "L\'e0m sao v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec, ch\u7881  l\'e0... nh\'e0 ch\'fa t\'f4i c\u361 ng \u7903  ph\'eda n\'e0y, nh\'ecn r\u7845 t quen m\u7855 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i: "Th\u7853 t l\'e0 tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p, thu\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ch\'fa m\u7897 t l\'e1t nh\'e9?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\'ean t\uc0\u7909 c xua tay: "Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n. Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 i qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y b\u7885 n h\u7885 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 i\u7873 u g\'ec, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\u432 \u7901 i, m\u7863 t m\'e0y vui v\u7867 , t\u7921 a h\u7891  r\u7845 t h\'e0i l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7845 t \'edt khi th\u7845 y h\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i tho\u7843 i m\'e1i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, t\u7921  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 m\'ecnh l\'e0m h\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y h\u7855 n, ch\u7881  ng\u7891 i \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean len l\'e9n nh\'ecn, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c h\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean th\u7853 t \u273 \u7865 p m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7899 i khi \u273 \u7871 n c\u7893 ng nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng xe, l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p, theo nh\u432  c\'e1ch n\'f3i th\u7901 i nay, nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7899 i nh\'e0 ch\'fa m\'ecnh qu\u7843  th\u7921 c c\'f3 th\u7875  coi l\'e0 m\u7897 t ti\u7875 u khu. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ni\'ean \u273 \u7841 i c\u7911 a t\'f2a nh\'e0 n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 ti\u7875 u khu, gi\'e1 ph\'f2ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 i\'ean cu\u7891 ng gi\u7889 ng hi\u7879 n gi\u7901 , kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch gi\u7919 a c\'e1c nh\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i r\u7845 t g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'eda t\'e2y b\uc0\u7855 c th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A l\'e0 n\'fai, tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \u7883 a th\u7871  nh\u7845 p nh\'f4, nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  g\u7847 n h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i nh\'e0 ch\'fa, l\'e0 \u7903  \u273 \u7881 nh cao nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a v\'f9ng n\'e0y, \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a h\u7847 u nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y t\u7915 ng ng\'f4i nh\'e0 n\u7857 m l\u7867  t\u7867  b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng chia l\'e0m ba l\u7847 u, l\u7899 n g\u7845 p \u273 \'f4i nh\'e0 ch\'fa, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i th\u259 m quan m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, ch\u7881  v\'e0o m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  l\u7847 u hai n\'f3i: "\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 ph\'f2ng t\'f4i, c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n \u7903  ph\'f2ng n\'e0o th\'ec c\u7913  ch\u7885 n t\'f9y \'fd."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u l\'fac \u273 i ra l\u7841 i thu\u7853 n tay ch\u7881  c\u259 n ph\'f2ng c\'e1ch v\'e1ch m\'ecnh n\'f3i: "\u7902  ph\'f2ng n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u7883  ngh\u7883  g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 To\'e0n b\uc0\u7897  c\u259 n nh\'e0 r\u7845 t l\u7899 n, l\u7841 i c\'f3 v\u7867  tr\u7889 ng tr\u7843 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7887 i: "C\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi "\u7914 " m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, b\u7893  sung: "Nh\'e0 n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 nh\'e0 t\'f4i, v\'ec v\'e0i nguy\'ean nh\'e2n n\'ean ch\u7911  nh\'e0 \u273 \'fang l\'fac cho t\'f4i m\u432 \u7907 n \u7903  th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi s\uc0\u7855 p x\u7871 p xong hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i c\'f9ng nhau l\'e1i xe \u273 i si\'eau th\u7883  g\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 mua \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m bi\u7871 t tr\'f9 ngh\u7879  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7845 t gi\u7887 i, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng s\u7869  mang c\'e1c lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n nh\u432  b\'e1nh bao, m\'f3n kho c\'e1c lo\u7841 i v\u7873  ph\'f2ng cho c\u7853 u, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t ngon, m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u c\'f2n r\u7845 t kinh ng\u7841 c, b\'e2y gi\u7901  th\'ec kh\'f4ng kinh ng\u7841 c n\u7919 a, ch\u7881  ng\u7891 i \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng \u259 n th\'e0nh th\'e0nh th\u7853 t th\u7853 t th\'e8m ch\u7843 y n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng ch\u7901 , c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quay v\u7873  nh\'e0 h\u7855 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 m\u7897 t quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh h\u7841 nh ph\'fac.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 n ph\'f2ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  cho c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u432 \u7907 n ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m trong ph\'f2ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\u7855 m r\u7917 a xong xu\'f4i m\u7899 i tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh. Gi\u432 \u7901 ng \'eam \'eam m\u7873 m m\u7873 m, h\u432 \u417 ng th\u417 m thoang tho\u7843 ng, h\u417 i gi\u7889 ng m\'f9i tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Ph\'f2ng cho kh\'e1ch kh\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903 , v\u7915 a r\u7891 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 \u273 em \u273 \u7891  d\'f9ng s\u7841 ch tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \'f4\u777 i sang gi\u432 \u7901 ng ph\'f2ng n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi chen ch\'fac ng\u7911  chung ba \u273 \'eam, r\u7845 t quen thu\u7897 c m\'f9i v\u7883  kia, kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u li\u7873 n ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7917 a \u273 \'eam c\u7853 u tho\'e1ng nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng c\u7885  s\'e0n x\u7897 t xo\u7841 t, m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng m\u7903  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 ang \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ra, \u273 ang c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7891  b\'f2 t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i v\'e0o, th\u7853 m ch\'ed m\u7897 t n\u7917 a th\'e2n th\u7875  \u273 \'e3 ti\u7871 n v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng, \u273 ang ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u c\u7889  g\u7855 ng nh\'ecn l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i nghe th\u7845 y \'e2m thanh "T\'ea t\'ea...\'ea...eeee" quen tai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843  kinh l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7853 t d\u7853 y, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ph\u7843 n x\u7841  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n g\'e0o l\u7899 n: "... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7853 u qua \u273 \'e2y! Xin c\u7853 u mau sang \u273 \'e2y..."\cb1 \
