\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u432  th\u7871  hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0 c\u7905  n\'e0o th\'e2n m\u7853 t, ch\u7881  m\u7897 t m\u7921 c th\u7915 a c\u417  tr\u7889 n trong ng\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\'ecnh ph\u7909 c t\'e2m tr\u7841 ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7911  kinh ho\u7843 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 ... V\u7915 a r\u7891 i th\u7913  kia th\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 ...\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\'fa, ch\'fang t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  l\u7897  h\'ecnh d\'e1ng di\u7879 n m\u7841 o, sau \u273 \'f3 \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y hai con qu\u7927  tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 , nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng ch\u7881  xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \u7903  ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3, kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 n th\'eam n\u7917 a b\u432 \u7899 c. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 l\u7847 n n\'e0y, th\u7913  n\'e0y, l\u7841 i nh\u7845 t m\u7921 c ti\u7871 n v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\u7921 a trong ng\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i ph\'e1t gi\'e1c h\u417 i x\u7845 u h\u7893 , \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t tho\'e1ng lui ra, \'e2m th\u7847 m m\u7915 ng v\'ec trong ph\'f2ng t\u7889 i ch\u7855 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi bu\'f4ng c\u7853 u ra, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "Kh\'e1 h\u417 n ch\'fat n\'e0o ch\u432 a? Kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 ? T\'f4i v\u7873  ph\'f2ng nh\'e9?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7915 ng, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7845 p \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7897  tho\'e1ng c\'e1i b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tay \'e1o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, sau khi b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean n\'f3i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i m\'ecnh v\uc0\u7851 n s\u7907 ? N\'f3i tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 i, b\u7891 i t\'f4i th\'eam l\'e1t n\u7919 a? Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ch\u7855 c c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 qua m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901 , b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t kinh ho\u7843 ng h\'f4 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta t\u7899 i th\'ec th\'f4i, sao c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c l\'f4i k\'e9o ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\'ednh t\'ecnh c\u361 ng th\u7853 t l\'e0 t\u7889 t, ki\'ean nh\u7851 n nh\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \u7913 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean ch\u7901 , t\'f9y \'fd c\u7853 u l\'f4i k\'e9o tay \'e1o m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai th\uc0\u7845 p \u273 \u7847 u, ch\u7853 m r\u7873  r\u7873  bu\'f4ng tay ra, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i thao t\'e1c c\u7921 c nhanh cu\u7889 n ch\u259 n gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh th\'e0nh m\u7897 t \u273 \u7889 ng \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, \u7845 p \'fang n\'f3i: "... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\'f4i sang ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u ng\u7911  chung v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng t\u7889 t, nghe v\u7853 y ch\u7859 ng nh\u7919 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'ea c\u7853 u nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n mang g\u7889 i, ch\u7895  t\'f4i c\'f3 hai c\'e1i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u ng\u7889 c ng\u7889 c \'f4m ch\u259 n \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i tinh th\u7847 n c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y g\'ec, b\'e2y gi\u7901  m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\u7899 i l\'fac n\'e3y s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c ch\'e2n t\'ea r\u7847 n, \u273 \u7913 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a t\'e9 xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 a tay \u273 \u7905  c\u7853 u, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\'eau ch\u7885 c c\u7853 u nghi\'eam t\'fac c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "C\'f3 mu\u7889 n t\'f4i b\u7871  c\u7853 u qua kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhanh ch\'f3ng l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, b\u7843 n th\'e2n ki\'ean c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, theo s\'e1t l\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7885 n sang ph\'f2ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  s\u7907  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u7903  chung v\u7899 i c\u7853 u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tuy r\u7857 ng s\u7889 ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, trong ph\'f2ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f4i m\u7897 t m\'e9t t\'e1m, \u273 \u7911  cho hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  ng\u7911 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7891 ng ch\u259 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, chi\u7871 m m\u7897 t ch\u7895  b\'ean ngo\'e0i. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7845 y c\u7853 u n\u7857 m xong li\u7873 n \u273 \u432 a tay t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\u7841 i l\'e2m v\'e0o trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \'e1nh tr\u259 ng m\'f4ng lung xuy\'ean qua r\'e8m c\u7917 a s\u7893  v\'e0ng nh\u7841 t chi\u7871 u v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7889 n quay l\u432 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y c\u7853 u m\u7903  m\u7855 t l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , k\u7871 t c\u7845 u hai ph\'f2ng nh\u432  nhau, theo \u273 \'f3 m\'e0u s\u7855 c v\'e0 hoa v\u259 n c\u7917 a c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng nhau, c\'e1i n\'e0y l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n v\u7915 a r\u7891 i, sau \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\'ecn m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, lu\'f4n s\u7907  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 b\'f2 \u273 \u7871 n. Nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i tuy r\u7857 ng nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 b\u7845 t an trong ng\u7921 c l\u7841 i c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng t\u259 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u7883 ch v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\'e1t sau l\u7841 i nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c d\u7883 ch v\u7873  ph\'eda h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra, nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng l\u7845 n v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh: "Sao c\'f2n ch\u432 a ng\u7911 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean xoay ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n chi\u7871 m di\u7879 n t\'edch gi\u432 \u7901 ng qu\'e1 l\u7899 n, nhanh ch\'f3ng lui v\u7873  ch\u7895  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'f3i: "... T\'f4i nh\'ecn c\u7917 a l\u7841 i nh\u7899  t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7907 , lo l\u7855 ng s\u7869  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 b\'f2 \u273 \u7871 n m\'e0 m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, n\'ean l\u7841 i nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\'ecn ti\u7871 p." V\'f2ng tu\u7847 n ho\'e0n \'e1c t\'ednh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi sau khi nghe xong kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7915 a \u273 \u7883 nh b\'e0y t\u7887  th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  "T\'f4i \u273 \'e2y quay v\u7873  th\'e0nh th\u7853 t ng\u7911  kh\'f4ng chen l\u7845 n c\u7853 u n\u7919 a", l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u432 \u417 n c\'e1nh tay qua, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p t\u432  th\u7871  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7863 t \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t \'f4m c\u7853 u k\u7873  c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895  v\u7899 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7843 n nhi\'ean n\'f3i: "V\u7853 y c\u7913  th\u7871  n\'e0y ng\u7911  \u273 i, m\u7863 t quay v\u7873  ph\'eda t\'f4i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. T\'f4i nh\'ecn c\u7917 a thay c\u7853 u r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\u7843 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'ecnh \uc0\u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i l\u7891 ng ng\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, m\u7863 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u432 \u7899 ng ra c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , c\'f3 v\u7867  \u273 \'edch x\'e1c r\u7845 t an to\'e0n... Tr\'ec Di\'ean luy\u7871 n ti\u7871 c kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n t\u7915  ch\u7889 i, l\'ean ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7853 u th\u7853 t t\u7889 t", sau \u273 \'f3 v\'f9i \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o v\u7883  tr\'ed t\u7889 t n\u7885  ng\u7911  m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'fac ng\uc0\u7911  m\u417  tay v\'f4 th\u7913 c v\u432 \u417 n ra, ch\u7889 ng l\'ean ng\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'e9o tay c\u7853 u kho\'e1c l\'ean c\u7893  m\'ecnh, tay kh\u7869  l\u432 \u7899 t qua vai v\'e0 l\u432 ng c\u7853 u, c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng n\u7881  non: "Ngoan, ng\u7911  \u273 i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i g\uc0\u7885 i l\'e0 qu\'e1 tam ba b\u7853 n, \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 l\u7847 n th\u7913  ba c\u7853 u g\u7863 p qu\u7927  trong th\u7901 i gian ng\u7855 n r\u7891 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o l\u7915 a m\'ecnh d\u7889 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh t\u297 nh l\u7841 i n\u7919 a, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\'f9y ti\u7879 n k\u7875  v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cha m\uc0\u7865  \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  H n\u417 i xa, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 nhi\u7873 u tu\u7893 i, t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7871  h\u7879  tr\u432 \u7899 c v\u7899 i th\u7871  h\u7879  m\'ecnh l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 gi\u7889 ng nhau, n\'f3i cho b\u7885 n h\u7885  bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  lo l\u7855 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng t\u7921  d\u432 ng c\'f2n sinh th\'eam chuy\u7879 n. B\u7841 n h\u7885 c b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng giao t\'ecnh kh\'f4ng s\'e2u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tin l\u7901 i m\'ecnh n\'f3i, ch\u7881  cho l\'e0 m\'ecnh b\u7883 a chuy\u7879 n l\'f2e ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c \u273 \'e3 \u7903  nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7889 n ng\'e0y, sau \u273 \'eam \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u y\'ean \u7893 n, kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t sinh chuy\u7879 n g\'ec n\u7919 a. Nh\u432 ng ban \u273 \'eam c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m m\u7897 t m\'ecnh quay v\u7873  ph\'f2ng cho kh\'e1ch b\'ean c\u7841 nh ng\u7911 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng nh\u7855 c c\u7853 u \u273 i, c\u7853 u li\u7873 n gi\u7843  b\u7897  nh\u432  kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  ra c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3, v\u7851 n t\u7887  v\u7867  t\u7921  nhi\'ean nh\u432  c\u361 , v\u7915 a \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 i ng\u7911  s\u7869  ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng t\u7899 i ph\'f2ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\'e1o danh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 an c\u432  l\u7841 c nghi\u7879 p \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, l\'e1 r\u7909 ng m\u7885 c r\u7877 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\u7921  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \'e2n t\'ecnh c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p c\'f4ng t\u7917  b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \u7875  b\'e1o \u273 \'e1p, v\'ec v\u7853 y m\u7895 i ng\'e0y h\u259 ng h\'e1i r\u7917 a b\'e1t lau nh\'e0, ngay c\u7843  qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \u7891  trong \u273 \u7891  ngo\'e0i c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7853 u c\u361 ng d\u7889 c s\u7913 c nh\u7853 n th\u7847 u, t\u7915  gi\u7863 t \u7911 i ph\u417 i n\u7855 ng \u273 \u7871 n g\u7845 p g\u7885 n l\u7841 i c\u7845 t v\'e0o trong t\u7911  to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7883 u tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng th\uc0\u7913  b\u7843 y, nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi c\u7853 u nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin nh\u7855 n h\u7865 n \u273 i ch\u417 i b\'f3ng r\u7893  c\u7911 a l\'e3o Vi\'ean. H\'f4m nay c\u7853 u v\u7889 n \u273 \u7883 nh quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n \u273 \u7875  l\u7845 y th\'eam qu\u7847 n \'e1o thay, ti\u7879 n th\u7875  t\u7899 i th\u432  vi\u7879 n m\u432 \u7907 n m\u7897 t \'edt t\'e0i li\u7879 u tham kh\u7843 o, c\u7897 ng th\'eam sau khi \u273 \u7855 n \u273 o suy ngh\u297  c\u7853 u c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n k\u7875  m\u7897 t ch\'fat chuy\u7879 n g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y v\u7899 i l\'e3o Vi\'ean, \u273 \u7875  l\'e3o Vi\'ean gi\'fap m\'ecnh ngh\u297  c\'e1ch, b\u7903 i v\u7853 y r\u7845 t vui v\u7867  m\'e0 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7921  \u273 \u7883 nh sau khi \u259 n s\'e1ng xong s\u7869  \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, d\u7863 n d\'f2: "Bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i nh\u7899  v\u7873  s\u7899 m m\u7897 t ch\'fat, t\'f4i l\'e0m l\u7849 u cho c\u7853 u \u259 n.\cb1 \
