\cb3 H\'f4m nay t\'e2m t\'ecnh Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\uc0\u7889 t l\u7855 m, ch\u417 i m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n xong \u273 \'e3 ra s\'e2n, c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t b\'ean xem th\'eam m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n n\u7919 a, n\'f3i v\u7899 i l\'e3o Vi\'ean m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng xong d\u7913 t kho\'e1t x\'e1ch balo \u273 i th\u432  vi\u7879 n m\u432 \u7907 n t\'e0i li\u7879 u mu\u7889 n d\'f9ng tr\u432 \u7899 c, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  thu d\u7885 n qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7847 n r\u7891 i m\u7899 i tr\u7903  l\u7841 i s\'e2n b\'f3ng. L\'fac n\'e0y m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 t\u7843 n \u273 i h\u7871 t, ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  d\u432 \u7899 i t\'e0ng c\'e2y trong s\'e2n th\u7875  d\u7909 c ch\u7901  c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y c\u7853 u xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n l\'e3o Vi\'ean li\u7873 n ti\u7871 n t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n, ch\u7881  v\'e0o balo c\u259 ng ph\u7891 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "L\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 nhi\u7873 u th\u7871 ? C\u7853 u \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 mu\u7889 n g\u7843  \u273 i h\u7917 m?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean che che balo: "... \uc0\u272 \u7915 ng c\'f3 n\'f3i linh tinh."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean nh\'ecn nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7901 i gian, \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883 : "Ngo\'e0i c\u7893 ng ph\'eda \u273 \'f4ng m\u7899 i m\u7903  m\u7897 t qu\'e1n l\u7849 u, h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y b\u7841 n b\'e8 t\'f4i l\'fac chat tr\'ean m\u7841 ng \u273 \u7873 u nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i, ch\'fang ta \u273 i th\u7917  kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat x\uc0\u7845 u h\u7893 , t\u7915  ch\u7889 i n\'f3i: "... H\'f4m nay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m l\u7849 u \u7903  nh\'e0, b\u7843 o t\'f4i v\u7873  \u259 n. H\u7865 n h\'f4m kh\'e1c nh\'e9?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng h\'e0i l\'f2ng nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng: "T\'f4i n\'f3i Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  g\u7843  \u273 i r\u7891 i \'e0? T\'f4i \u273 \'e3 b\u7843 o h\'f4m nay c\u7853 u th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\u417 i n\u7893 i m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n, h\'f3a ra l\'e0 th\u7853 n h\u432 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng c\'f3 n\'f3i lung tung!" T\'f4i m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng... gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7853 u n\'f3i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean than th\u7903  trong b\u7909 ng, v\u7915 a m\u7901 i l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 \u7871 n qu\'e1n c\'e0 ph\'ea d\u432 \u7899 i c\u259 ng tin g\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 v\u7915 a gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'f3i, "T\'f4i \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i qu\u7927 . \u272 ang mu\u7889 n k\u7875  v\u7899 i c\u7853 u h\u7887 i c\u7853 u xem c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "G\uc0\u7863 p qu\u7927 ? Kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o?" L\'e3o Vi\'ean theo s\'e1t c\u7853 u h\u7887 i t\u7881  m\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0o qu\'e1n c\'e0 ph\'ea ng\u7891 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7885 i hai ly c\'e0 ph\'ea, k\u7875  t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n \u273 u\'f4i chuy\u7879 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n sau \u273 \'eam nghe tin c\'f4 g\'e1i kia b\u7883  ng\u7897  h\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y n\u7919  qu\u7927  c\'f9ng v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 tr\u7843 i qua cho \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean v\uc0\u7899 i c\u7853 u l\'e0 giao t\'ecnh b\u7889 n n\u259 m \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c c\'f9ng nhau tr\u7889 n h\u7885 c c\'f9ng nhau ch\'e9p b\'e0i c\'f9ng nhau ch\u417 i game c\'f9ng nhau tr\u432 \u7899 c khi thi n\u432 \u7899 c t\u7899 i ch\'e2n m\u7899 i nh\u7843 y, sau khi nghe xong qu\u7843  nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ho\'e0i nghi Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7841 t m\'ecnh, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i lo l\u7855 ng n\'f3i: "Vi\u7879 c n\'e0y kh\'f4ng d\u7877  x\u7917  l\'fd. \u272 \u7847 u ti\'ean ch\'fang ta kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 khoa h\u7885 c hay huy\u7873 n h\u7885 c, l\'e0 do c\u7853 u b\u7903 i v\'e0i nguy\'ean nh\'e2n sinh ra \u7843 o gi\'e1c hay l\'e0 'Nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia' x\'e1c th\u7921 c t\u7891 n t\u7841 i, h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng t\'ecm t\u7899 i c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "T\'f4i c\u361 ng hy v\u7885 ng l\'e0 khoa h\u7885 c c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7843 i th\'edch, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c c\u7911 a t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 ang suy ngh\u297  g\'ec, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean v\u7895  \u273 \'f9i n\'f3i: "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, t\'f4i nh\u7899  ra r\u7891 i, t\'f4i c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7857 ng b\u7841 n c\u7845 p hai, n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n ta c\u361 ng th\'e2n thi\u7871 t l\u7855 m. H\u7891 i c\u7845 p ba l\'fac g\u7863 p l\u7841 i t\'f4i t\u7915 ng nghe h\u7855 n nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 b\'e1i s\u432 , \u273 i h\u7885 c m\u7845 y th\u7913  th\u7847 n th\u7847 n qu\u7927  qu\u7927  n\'e0y, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i h\u7887 i h\u7855 n xem h\u7855 n c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'f4ng. N\u7871 u h\u7855 n x\u7917  l\'fd \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t, kh\'f4ng x\u7917  l\'fd \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec ch\u7855 c c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7881  c\u7853 u t\'ecm nh\u7919 ng cao nh\'e2n kh\'e1c, \'edt nh\u7845 t s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7883  l\u7915 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng tr\u7885 ng c\u7893  khinh kim, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe n\'f3i l\'e0 b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7911 a l\'e3o Vi\'ean, nh\u432 ng tu\u7893 i b\u7857 ng m\'ecnh l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng y\'ean t\'e2m l\u7855 m, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u l\'e3o Vi\'ean n\'f3i r\u7845 t c\'f3 l\'fd, c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u7901  Vi\'ean gi\'fap h\u7865 n g\u7863 p ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n h\u7885 c n\'e0y, b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\u7845 y th\u7901 i gian kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7899 m li\u7873 n nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 \'e1p t\'e0u \u273 i\u7879 n ng\u7847 m v\u7873  nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac c\uc0\u7853 u \u7845 n chu\'f4ng c\u7917 a th\'ec \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 7:40' t\u7889 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 n\u7845 u xong n\u432 \u7899 c d\'f9ng, b\'e0y k\'edn m\u7897 t b\'e0n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, sau khi m\u7903  c\u7917 a cho c\u7853 u li\u7873 n nh\u7855 c c\u7853 u r\u7917 a tay r\u7891 i ng\u7891 i v\'e0o b\'e0n, b\u7843 o c\u7853 u \u259 n xong th\'ec thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nguy\'ean li\uc0\u7879 u n\u7845 u l\u7849 u c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0 x\u432 \u417 ng tr\'e2u h\u7855 n \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  ninh, h\u7847 m v\u7899 i \u7899 t v\'e0 hoa ti\'eau tr\u7891 ng \u7903  v\'f9ng T\u7913  Xuy\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t v\u7853 n chuy\u7875 n \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A, \u259 n v\'e0o t\'ea cay th\u417 m ngon, d\u432  v\u7883  v\'f4 c\'f9ng. K\u7871 t h\u7907 p v\u7899 i th\u7883 t b\'f2 th\u7883 t d\'ea, t\'f4m c\'e1 t\u432 \u417 i m\u7899 i, d\u7841  d\'e0y b\'f2 s\'e1ch b\'f2 tr\u7913 ng chim c\'fat, c\'e1c lo\u7841 i rau qu\u7843  s\u7841 ch, c\'f3 c\u7843  mi\u7871 n, ch\'e2n gi\'f2 hun kh\'f3i, c\'e1c lo\u7841 i th\u7913 c \u259 n nh\u7865 , m\u7895 i lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t \'edt, nh\'ecn r\u7845 t tinh t\u7871 , nh\u432 ng m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng thi\u7871 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u259 n g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng d\u7915 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7901 i thu m\'e1t m\u7867 , \u273 \'fang l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m th\'edch h\u7907 p \u273 \u7875  \u259 n l\u7849 u nh\u7845 t. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i l\u7845 y hai chai bia \u432 \u7899 p l\u7841 nh v\u7915 a kh\'e9o t\u7915  trong t\u7911  l\u7841 nh ra, r\'f3t cho m\'ecnh v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t c\u7889 c. Bia m\'e1t l\u7841 nh v\'e0o b\u7909 ng c\'e0ng th\'eam s\u7843 ng kho\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u259 n \u273 \u7871 n vui s\u432 \u7899 ng, ngay c\u7843  l\'fac n\'f3i c\u361 ng \u259 n, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y l\'f2ng \u273 \u7847 y lo s\u7907  c\u361 ng t\u7841 m th\u7901 i b\u7883  n\'e9m qua m\u7897 t b\'ean, b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c \u273 \'e3 \u259 n v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u gi\'fap Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi thu d\u7885 n b\'e0n, v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m t\u7855 m r\u7917 a, sau \u273 \'f3 d\'f9ng m\'e1y gi\u7863 t gi\u7863 t s\u7841 ch qu\u7847 n \'e1o d\'ednh \u273 \u7847 y m\'f9i l\u7849 u v\'e0 m\'f9i bia c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i \u273 em ph\u417 i, b\u7845 y gi\u7901  m\u7899 i \u273 i s\u7855 p x\u7871 p m\u7897 t balo b\u7921  qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ng\u7911  trong ph\'f2ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u432 ng qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7853 u mang t\u7899 i v\u7851 n treo trong t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o trong c\u259 n ph\'f2ng kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o kia ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng c\u361 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i c\u361 , t\'f4ng m\'e0u g\u7895 , c\'f3 hai c\'e1nh t\u7911 , cao t\u7847 m m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\'ecn qua ph\u7849 m ch\u7845 t r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t d\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n c\'f3 ch\'fat s\u7907  c\u259 n ph\'f2ng \u273 \'f3, sau khi v\'e0o c\u7917 a vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean l\'e0 b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n l\'ean, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7875  balo c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o k\'e9o m\u7897 t c\'e1nh t\u7911  ra chu\u7849 n b\u7883  treo qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong t\uc0\u7911  c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7913  \u273 \u7887  t\u432 \u417 i nh\u432  m\'e1u \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng, m\'e1u th\u7883 t l\u7851 n l\u7897 n, mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean "R\uc0\u7847 m" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng theo ph\u7843 n x\u7841  \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a t\u7911  l\u7841 i, ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng ra ngo\'e0i, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh theo ti\u7871 ng n\u432 \u7899 c x\'f4ng v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac m\'ecnh v\u7873  ph\'f2ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7915 a m\u7899 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m t\u7855 m r\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n \u273 ang \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, to\'e0n th\'e2n h\u7855 n \u432 \u7899 t s\u361 ng, t\'f3c \u273 en ng\u7855 n d\'ednh s\'e1t m\u7863 t, n\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915  v\'f2i hoa sen phun xu\u7889 ng to\'e0n th\'e2n, d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m, m\u7895 i gi\u7885 t n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7873 u ph\u7843 n x\u7841  \'e1nh kim l\u7845 p lo\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7891 i l\u7841 i b\u7845 t ch\u7845 p nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, sau khi x\'f4ng v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m li\u7873 n tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p x\'f4 v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f2ng n\uc0\u432 \u7899 c \u7845 m \'e1p d\u7897 i l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, x\u7889 i \u432 \u7899 t h\u7871 t \'e1o c\u7853 u, nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng g\u7885 i hai ph\u7847 n l\'fd tr\'ed c\u7911 a c\u7853 u quay v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t tay \u273 \u7905  l\u7845 y h\'f4ng c\u7853 u \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u7853 u, t\u7855 t v\'f2i sen, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u h\u7887 i: "X\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i l\uc0\u7841 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y th\u7913  kia, l\u7847 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 da... Ngay trong t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o ph\'f2ng b\'ean, t\'f4i v\u7915 a m\u7903  ra \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7855 p b\u7855 p n\'f3i, r\u259 ng v\u7851 n va l\u7853 p c\u7853 p r\'f9ng m\'ecnh, \u7899 n l\u7841 nh t\u7915  \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng \'f9a l\'ean k\'edch th\'edch to\'e0n th\'e2n c\u7853 u ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, d\u7913 t kho\'e1t c\u7903 i to\'e0n b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u432 \u7899 t \u273 \u7851 m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u ra n\'e9m sang b\u7879  b\'ean c\u7841 nh, k\'e9o c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n d\u432 \u7899 i v\'f2i sen m\u7903  l\u7841 i n\u432 \u7899 c, xoay b\'ean n\u432 \u7899 c \u7845 m cho c\u7853 u g\u7897 t r\u7917 a. B\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh nh\'ecn, ch\u7881  v\u7851 n d\'f9ng tay tr\'e1i \u273 \u7905  c\u7853 u tr\'e1nh cho c\u7853 u ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng, trong mi\u7879 ng nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng tr\u7845 n an: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, c\u7853 u t\u7855 m n\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3ng \u273 i, d\u7883 u \u273 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, t\u7849 y s\u7841 ch h\u7889 i kh\'ed, t\'f4i qua \u273 \'f3 xem th\u7917  xem sao."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c tr\u7903  tay k\'e9o tay h\u7855 n: "... \u272 \u7915 ng, t\'f4i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u c\'f9ng \u273 i."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng mang qu\uc0\u7847 n \'e1o sang, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi li\u7873 n l\u7845 y lu\'f4n hai b\u7897  \u273 \u7891  ng\u7911  s\u7841 ch s\u7869  trong t\u7911  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, m\u7897 t b\u7897  h\u7855 n m\u7863 c, m\u7897 t b\u7897  n\'e9m cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f3c ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng cao nh\u432  h\u7855 n, \'e1o bu\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n m\'f4ng, qu\u7847 n c\'f2n ph\u7843 i x\u7855 n l\'ean m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7851 n c\u7853 u sang ph\'f2ng b\'ean, b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o m\u7903  ra nh\'ecn th\u7917 , n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 i v\'e0o \u273 ang \u7903  \u273 \u7913 ng c\u7917 a nh\'ecn: "A Di\'ean, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec c\u7843 , \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng l\'fac n\'e3y l\u7841 i nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c run run, l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  n\'f3i: "Th\u7853 t, th\u7853 t sao..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi "\u7914 " m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907 . Chi\u7871 c t\u7911  n\'e0y c\u361 ng c\'f3 l\'e2u l\u7855 m r\u7891 i, s\'e1ng mai t\'f4i t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 em \u273 i thay m\u7899 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907 . Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean t\'f4i l\u7845 y qu\u7847 n \'e1o b\'ean trong c\u7911 a c\u7853 u treo v\'e0o t\u7911  ph\'f2ng t\'f4i nh\'e9?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i qua c\u7847 m l\u7845 y ba l\'f4 \u273 \u7875  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh, l\'f2ng c\'f2n ho\u7843 ng m\'e0 nh\'ecn chi\u7871 c t\u7911  m\'e0u g\u7895  n\u7863 ng n\u7873  c\u361  k\u7929  kia, l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "... Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n, t\'f4i mang balo n\'e0y \u273 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, b\'ean trong c\'f3 qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \u7875  thay r\u7891 i. Qu\u7847 n \'e1o trong \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 gi\'fap c\u7853 u l\u7845 y ra th\'ec c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m gi\u7919  l\u7841 i nh\u7919 ng b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \'f3 n\u7919 a, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u qu\u7847 n \'e1o b\'ean trong v\u7889 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\u7897  v\u7899 i m\u7845 y chi\u7871 c qu\u7847 n l\'f3t l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u mang \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'f4m balo c\uc0\u7911 a m\'ecnh, l\u7841 i c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng h\u7855 n, c\u7853 u \'e2m th\u7847 m ph\'e1t th\u7879  b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng bao gi\u7901  \u273 i v\'e0o c\u259 n ph\'f2ng \u273 \'f3 n\u7919 a. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7885 n n\u7917 a t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \u7875  cho c\u7853 u treo. Ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7911  tr\u7919  \u273 \u7891 , hai t\u7911  \u273 \u7873 u treo qu\u7847 n \'e1o th\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7863 c m\u7897 t m\'f9a, cho n\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c qu\'e1 ch\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean treo t\uc0\u7915 ng m\'f3n t\u7915 ng m\'f3n v\'e0o trong t\u7911  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\'ecn qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i treo song song c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i d\u7921 a tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u b\u7853 n r\u7897 n, tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u g\u7889 i \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t quy\u7875 n s\'e1ch, m\u7863 t m\'e0y cong cong, l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i li\u7873 n c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7885 c s\'e1ch, b\u7897  d\'e1ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7885 c \u273 \u7871 n say m\'ea h\'e0i l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\'f2 m\'f2 c\uc0\u7889  \'fd l\u7841 i g\u7847 n nh\'ecn t\'ean quy\u7875 n s\'e1ch kia, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n l\'e0 cu\u7889 n
