\f1 l\uc0\u7841 i, h\u7887 i c\u7853 u c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7855 n \u273 \u432 a ra ph\u432 \u417 ng \'e1n th\u7913  t\u432 : "C\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ng\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\u7841 i b\u7893  sung: "Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u h\'ecnh nh\u432  t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1i n\'e0o m\u7899 i, \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 gi\u7863 t r\u7845 t s\u7841 ch r\u7891 i ... C\u7853 u c\'f3 \u273 \u7875  \'fd kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7845 n an n\'f3i: "K\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u7853 u c\u7913  gi\u7919  nguy\'ean th\u7871  n\'e0y t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t ra sau khi t\u7855 m c\'f3 th\u7875  d\'f9ng m\'e1y s\u7845 y t\'f3c, r\u7845 t nhanh s\u7869  kh\'f4, hu\u7889 ng chi nh\'e0 h\u7855 n c\'f2n c\'f3 m\'e1y s\u7845 y chuy\'ean d\u7909 ng. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi y\'ean l\u7863 ng \u273 \u7863 t s\'e1ch xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, l\'e0m b\u7897  nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean t\u7845 t c\u7843  thi\u7871 t b\u7883  hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7841 i trong nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau sau khi t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0m l\'e0 g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n cho l\'e3o Vi\'ean, h\u7887 i th\u259 m chuy\u7879 n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7845 p hai kia. Cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y qu\'e1 k\'edch th\'edch qu\'e1 kinh h\'e3i r\u7891 i, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  c\u7913  b\'e1m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e3i kh\'f4ng tha, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh m\'ecnh th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u lo l\u7855 ng ch\u7901  tin nh\u7855 n, nh\u7899  ra l\'e3o Vi\'ean b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7853 y s\u7899 m th\u7871  n\'e0y m\u7899 i mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng sinh ra hai ph\u7847 n ki\'ean nh\u7851 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i l\'e3o Vi\'ean l\u7847 n n\'e0y v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i r\u7845 t n\u7875  t\'ecnh d\u7853 y r\u7845 t s\u7899 m, sau khi th\u7845 y tin nh\u7855 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 g\u7885 i th\u7859 ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u c\'f3 \u7903  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng?" L\'e3o Vi\'ean \u7903  b\'ean kia \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \u7903  trong b\u7871 p b\u7853 n r\u7897 n l\'e0m b\u7919 a s\'e1ng, tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "Kh\'f4ng, t\'f4i \u273 ang \u7903  v\u7899 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng l\'e3o Vi\'ean th\'f4ng qua s\'f3ng di \u273 \u7897 ng truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n: "T\u7889 t l\u7855 m, t\'f4i n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907  nha, t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7913 ng g\u7847 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ta m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "Chuy\uc0\u7879 n h\'f4m qua c\u7853 u n\'f3i cho t\'f4i t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u ghi nh\u7899 , ban n\'e3y t\'f4i v\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t tin, n\'f3i l\'e0 c\u7843 nh s\'e1t l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra hai thi th\u7875  trong m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng tr\u7885  g\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng ch\'fang ta, m\u7897 t kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ch\'e2n, b\u7883  gi\u7845 u d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng; m\u7897 t b\u7883 , b\u7883  l\u7897 t da... gi\u7845 u trong t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o."\cb1 \
\cb3 "... Thi th\uc0\u7875  kh\'f4ng ch\'e2n nghe n\'f3i \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t g\u7847 n m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i kh\u7899 p v\u7899 i h\'ecnh d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 c\u7853 u n\'f3i l\'e0 c\u7853 u tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u432 . Thi th\u7875  kh\'f4ng da v\u7915 a m\u7845 t m\u7841 ng h\'f4m qua, t\'f4i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ngh\u297  chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n c\u7853 u g\u7863 p qu\u7927  c\'f3 \u273 \'fang l\'e0 c\'f3 quan h\u7879  hay kh\'f4ng..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng l\'e3o Vi\'ean v\u7851 n truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n t\u7915  trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c c\u7847 m kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i tho\'e1ng c\'e1i r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng b\'e0n \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Sao th\u7871 ? B\u7841 n c\u7853 u n\'f3i g\'ec v\u7899 i c\u7853 u v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec... L\'e1t n\uc0\u7919 a s\u7869  n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u sau." Tr\'ec Di\'ean run r\u7849 y \u273 \'e1p Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, mi\u7879 ng k\'eau kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, \'e1nh m\u7855 t l\u7841 i r\'f5 r\'e0ng s\u7907  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7855 t l\u7917 a, b\u432 ng hai qu\u7843  tr\u7913 ng \u7889 p la ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, im l\u7863 ng an \u7911 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7899 i l\u7845 y d\u361 ng kh\'ed nh\u7863 t l\u7841 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, nghe th\u7845 y l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 \u7847 u b\'ean kia h\u7887 i th\u259 m: "N\'e0y, Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 ? L\'e0m sao th\u7871 ? V\u7915 a x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec, ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 s\u7907  n\'ean l\'e0m r\u417 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i th\'f4i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7889  h\u7871 t s\u7913 c tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh tr\u7843  l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean an \uc0\u7911 i c\u7853 u hai c\'e2u, n\'f3i ti\u7871 p: "T\'f4i h\u7887 i b\u7841 n t\'f4i r\u7891 i, t\'f4i k\u7875  s\u417  qua t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, h\u7855 n c\'f3 vi\u7879 c kh\'f4ng qua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, v\u7899 i l\u7841 i c\u361 ng n\'f3i h\u7855 n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n n\'f3i s\u432  t\u7927  h\u7855 n hai ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'fang d\u7883 p c\'f3 vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A, s\u432  t\u7927  h\u7855 n chuy\'ean \u273 \u7843 m nhi\u7879 m nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c th\u7871  n\'e0y, c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh h\u417 n h\u7855 n nhi\u7873 u, t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 nh\u7901  h\u7855 n h\u7865 n ch\u7883  \u7845 y r\u7891 i, s\u7855 p t\u7899 i h\u7859 n l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  g\u7863 p. C\u7853 u ki\'ean tr\'ec hai ng\'e0y n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e1p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7843 m \u417 n l\'e3o Vi\'ean v\'e0 b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n xong m\u7899 i c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i cho h\u7855 n nghe tin t\u7913 c v\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  ch\u7895  l\'e3o Vi\'ean. C\u7853 u ch\u7885 c ch\u7885 c tr\u7913 ng \u7889 p la ngo\'e0i ch\'edn trong m\u7873 m tr\'ean b\'e0n, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7897 t ch\'fat kh\u7849 u v\u7883  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n cho t\u7899 i b\'e2y gi\u7901 , c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\'e0 \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i t\'e0, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 ch\u7885 c ph\u7843 i ai g\'e2y ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o, th\u7843 m \'e1n gi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i li\'ean ti\u7871 p n\'e0y v\'ec sao ph\u7843 i d\'ednh l\'edu t\u7899 i m\'ecnh?\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7853 u ngh\u297 , ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  hung th\u7911  v\u7899 i m\'ecnh c\'f3 li\'ean quan?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875 ? \u7902  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A c\u7853 u quen bi\u7871 t r\u7845 t \'edt, giao thi\u7879 p ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'e0 ch\'fa, th\u7847 y gi\'e1o v\'e0 c\'e1c b\u7841 n h\u7885 c, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 quan h\u7879  v\u7899 i lo\u7841 i th\u7843 m \'e1n hung t\'e0n \u273 \u7871 n c\u7921 c \u273 i\u7875 m kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m v\u7873  k\'ed t\'fac x\'e1 \u7903 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh tr\u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \'f3, th\u7913  hai c\u7853 u quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i h\u7885 c, sau khi tan h\u7885 c l\u7841 i t\u7921  gi\'e1c tr\u7903  l\u7841 i nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. B\u7903 i v\'ec x\u7845 u h\u7893  m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u259 n nh\u7901  \u7903  \u273 \u7853 u, l\'fac v\u7873  c\u7853 u c\'f2n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 i si\'eau th\u7883  mua kh\'f4ng \'edt r\u432 \u7907 u v\'e0 nguy\'ean li\u7879 u n\u7845 u \u259 n x\'e1ch v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Chi\uc0\u7873 u t\u7889 i th\u7913  ba, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin nh\u7855 n l\'e3o Vi\'ean g\u7917 i t\u7899 i, n\'f3i l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 h\u7865 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7883  s\u432  t\u7927  kia, tr\u432 a th\u7913  t\u432  g\u7863 p h\u7865 n \u7903  qu\'e1n l\u7849 u ngo\'e0i c\u7893 ng ph\'eda \u273 \'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi sau khi nghe n\'f3i li\u7873 n b\'e0y t\u7887  th\u7913  t\u432  h\u7855 n c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7915 a \u273 \'fang l\'fac c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 i h\'f4m qua Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7911  qu\'e1 ngon, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m \u273 \u7873 u d\u7853 y tr\u7877 , l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7903  m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y tr\u7901 i s\'e1ng choang, c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i nh\'ecn, v\u7853 y m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m ph\'fat, c\u7853 u v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y lay c\'e1nh tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7885 i h\u7855 n t\u7881 nh, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 \'e1nh r\u259 ng r\u7917 a m\u7863 t, ngay c\u7843  \u273 i\u7875 m t\'e2m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u259 n, c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac ra kh\u7887 i nh\'e0 \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901  k\'e9m m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 May m\'e0 l\'fac n\'e0y tr\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 k\u7865 t xe, nh\u432 ng l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7871 n qu\'e1n l\u7849 u \u273 \'e3 h\u7865 n, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng xu\u7889 ng xe t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi xong \u273 i v\'e0o, l\'e3o Vi\'ean v\'e0 s\u432  t\u7927  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7883  s\u432  t\u7927  kia t\u7921  x\u432 ng h\u7885  H\u7891 , t\'ean Tinh, t\'f3c \u273 en c\u7855 t ng\u7855 n g\u7885 n g\'e0ng, nh\'ecn c\u361 ng r\u7845 t tr\u7867 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u7881  m\u7899 i ba m\u432 \u417 i, ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch kh\'e1 l\u7899 n so v\u7899 i h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7907 ng s\u432  th\'e1i Nga Mi trong t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean gi\uc0\u7899 i thi\u7879 u hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i nhau, thu x\u7871 p \u273 \u7875  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u259 n tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\'e1n l\uc0\u7849 u ngo\'e0i c\u7893 ng ph\'eda \u273 \'f4ng n\'e0y n\u7893 i danh \u7903  ch\u7895  ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c b\'e0y bi\u7879 n th\u7913 c \u259 n \u273 \u7897 c \u273 \'e1o s\'e1ng t\u7841 o, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  d\'f9ng v\'e1n g\u7895  d\'e0i n\u7917 a th\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0y th\u7883 t d\'ea, l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta t\u7915  th\u7883  gi\'e1c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7887 a m\'e3n; v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  x\u7871 p th\u7883 t d\'ea th\u7883 t b\'f2 th\'e0nh qu\u7847 n \'e1o cho b\'fap b\'ea Barbie. Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7871 m th\u7917  m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tuy r\u7857 ng m\'f9i v\u7883  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n k\'e9m xa so v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m \u7903  nh\'e0, trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\u7913 ng \u259 n qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi ba ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u H\u7891  Tinh m\u7899 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i ch\'ednh s\u7921 , c\'f4 nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 th\u7875  x\u432 ng h\'f4 nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? Chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 nghe l\'e3o Vi\'ean n\'f3i s\u417  qua r\u7891 i, t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p, t\'f4i s\u7869  n\'f3i k\u297  h\u417 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u h\u417 n sau."\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i quay sang l\'e3o Vi\'ean n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u Vi\'ean, chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec li\'ean quan t\u7899 i c\u7853 u, c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng li\'ean l\u7909 y v\'e0o th\'ec kh\'f4ng n\'ean li\'ean l\u7909 y v\'e0o, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\'f4i, quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng nghe ra \'fd t\u7913  trong l\u7901 i n\'f3i c\u7911 a v\u7883  H\u7891  s\u432  t\u7927  n\'e0y, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i l\'e3o Vi\'ean n\'f3i: "L\'e3o Vi\'ean c\u7853 u y\'ean t\'e2m, c\u7913  v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i, tr\'e1nh cho \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac c\'f3 m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c ngo\'e0i \'fd mu\u7889 n l\u7841 i k\'e9o c\u7843  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fang ta v\'e0o, ngay c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'e1o c\u7843 nh s\'e1t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean l\uc0\u7849 m b\u7849 m trong mi\u7879 ng: "S\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7913 ." Nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n nghe l\u7901 i x\'e1ch balo c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 i ra.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y H\uc0\u7891  Tinh m\u7899 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "L\u7847 n n\'e0y t\'f4i t\u7899 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A nguy\'ean nh\'e2n ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 v\'ec nh\u7919 ng v\u7909  \'e1n li\'ean ti\u7871 p ph\'e1t sinh m\u7845 y ng\'e0y qua, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i v\u7915 a \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e3 nghe s\u432  \u273 \u7879  n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "... T\'f4i c\uc0\u417  b\u7843 n c\'f3 th\u7875  k\u7871 t lu\u7853 n, g\'e2y \'e1n l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\'e0 l\'e0 y\'eau qu\'e1i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1ch l\'e0n kh\'f3i v\uc0\u7845 n v\'edt tr\'ean b\u7871 p l\u7849 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i c\'f4 g\'e1i \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t h\u7865 p d\'e0i m\'ea ho\u7863 c ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng b\'ecnh t\u297 nh tr\u7847 n thu\u7853 t l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7843  kinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Y\'eau qu\'e1i?" C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f3 tin l\u7863 p l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n. D\'f9 nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n li\'ean ti\u7871 p g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f3 b\u7873  t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tin tr\'ean th\u7871  gian n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i t\u7891 n t\u7841 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "Ph\u7843 i, y\'eau qu\'e1i c\u7853 u t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng so v\u7899 i y\'eau qu\'e1i trong th\u7847 n tho\u7841 i c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 gi\u7889 ng nhau. \u272 \u7875  t\'f4i cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t v\'ed d\u7909 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7901 i d\'e2n qu\u7889 c chi\u7871 n lo\u7841 n kh\u7855 p n\u417 i, thi\'ean h\u7841  r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng y\'ean \u7893 n, ph\'fac h\u7885 a *b\u297  th\'e1i c\'e1c lo\u7841 i kh\'ed v\u7853 n \u273 an xen v\'e0o nhau. V\'f9ng s\u417 n d\'e3 t\u7881 nh D c\'f3 t\u432 \u7907 ng d\'e3 th\u7847 n, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t x\'e2y d\u7921 ng t\u7915  khi n\'e0o, th\u7901 i k\'ec lo\u7841 n l\u7841 c kh\'f4ng ai t\u7871  b\'e1i, mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n d\u7847 n d\u7847 n suy vi b\u7883  b\u7887  qu\'ean. V\u7873  sau t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n th\u7845 y m\'e1u \u273 \u7893  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, h\u7845 p th\u7909  t\'e0 kh\'ed, li\u7873 n c\'f3 y\'eau t\'e0 b\'e1m v\'e0o t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n \u273 \'f3 l\u7845 y l\'e0m th\'e2n th\u7875  g\u7889 c m\'e0 sinh."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (b\uc0\u297  th\'e1i: B\u297  v\'e0 Th\'e1i l\'e0 hai qu\u7867  trong Kinh D\u7883 ch, B\u297  t\u432 \u7907 ng tr\u432 ng cho c\'f9ng kh\u7889 n, Th\'e1i t\u432 \u7907 ng tr\u432 ng cho s\u7921  hanh th\'f4ng.)
