\cb3 "L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i ch\u7841 y n\u7841 n qua, sau khi tr\u7901 i t\u7889 i li\u7873 n t\'e1 t\'fac trong mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n \u273 \u7893  n\'e1t, n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7855 t t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ch\u7843 y huy\u7871 t l\u7879 , m\u7903  to mi\u7879 ng, nhe r\u259 ng m\'e0 c\u432 \u7901 i, trong mi\u7879 ng \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 r\u259 ng nanh d\'e0i nh\u432  ng\'f3n tay. Nh\'f3m ng\u432 \u7901 i kia t\u7915 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t b\u7883  t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n h\'fat \u259 n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i xem x\'e9t t\'ecnh h\'ecnh b\u7887  ch\u7841 y s\u7899 m m\'e0 tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ki\u7871 p, sau khi ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 n k\u7875  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i xung quanh. V\u7873  sau l\u7841 i ph\'e1t sinh th\'eam m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n, g\'e2y \u7891 n \'e0o l\u7899 n r\u7891 i m\u7899 i m\u7901 i cao nh\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n b\u7855 t y\'eau t\'e0 n\u7885 . Th\u7913  g\'e2y \'e1n l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\'f9ng t\'ednh ch\u7845 t v\u7899 i t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n t\'f4i k\u7875  cho c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Hi\uc0\u7879 n gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\'ecn t\u7915  t\u7917  tr\u7841 ng, t\'f4i \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'f3 mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 "N\'f3 mu\uc0\u7889 n gom cho m\'ecnh m\u7897 t th\'e2n th\u7875 ."\cb1 \
