\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i k\u7867  ch\u7871 t thay, *\u273 o\u7841 t x\'e1... nh\u432 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i d\'f9ng ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c "gom" th\'e2n th\u7875  n\'e0y. Gom nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o? N\u7889 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  l\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gom \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'e0nh m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0?\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (\uc0\u273 o\u7841 t x\'e1: chi\u7871 m th\'e2n x\'e1c ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7875  s\u7889 ng l\u7841 i)
