\cb3 "N\'f3i ch\'ednh x\'e1c h\uc0\u417 n l\'e0 *t\'ecm k\'fd th\u7875 ." H\u7891  Tinh n\'f3i, "Gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\'f4i v\u7915 a m\u7899 i n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7845 y, lo\u7841 i y\'eau linh n\'e0y b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng d\u7921 a v\'e0o nh\u7919 ng v\u7853 t th\u7875  c\'f3 h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 sinh, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n, b\'fap b\'ea, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 tranh v\u7869  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i. B\u7903 i v\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0 lo\'e0i c\'f3 linh t\'ednh nh\u7845 t trong v\u7841 n v\u7853 t, v\u7853 t ch\u7871 t c\'f3 h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'ednh m\'e1u l\u7841 i b\u7883  t\'e0 kh\'ed o\'e1n kh\'ed b\'e1m v\'e0o s\u7869  r\u7845 t d\u7877  sinh ra y\'eau t\'e0 nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Th\u7913  n\'f3 b\'e1m v\'e0o c\u361 ng s\u7869  b\u7883  n\'f3 cho l\'e0 th\u7921 c th\u7875  c\u7911 a n\'f3."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (T\'ecm k\'fd th\uc0\u7875 : t\'ecm th\'e2n th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  b\'e1m v\'e0o)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 "N\uc0\u7871 u y\'eau t\'e0 t\'e0 kh\'ed qu\'e1 m\u7841 nh, c\'f3 l\u7869  n\'f3 kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n k\'fd th\u7875  c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  m\'ecnh ng\u432 ng t\u7909  ra th\u7921 c th\u7875  m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ti\'eau t\'e1n, nh\u432 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u7921 c k\'ec \'edt, c\u417  b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng t\u7891 n t\u7841 i. Nh\u432 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y l\u7841 i r\u7845 t k\u7923  qu\'e1i, sau khi \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A ti\u7871 p x\'fac thi th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i, t\'f4i v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'e0 kh\'ed th\u7913  kia l\u432 u l\u7841 i, t\'e0 kh\'ed c\u7911 a n\'f3 v\'f4 c\'f9ng d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n ngang ng\u432 \u7907 c, nh\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\u7841 i mu\u7889 n t\u7841 o ra k\'fd th\u7875  cho m\'ecnh... V\'ec v\u7853 y t\'f4i \u273 o\'e1n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3 h\u7859 n l\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7921 c th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  b\'e1m v\'e0o, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n d\u7921 a v\'e0o b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\'f3 \u273 \u7911  t\'e0 kh\'ed ng\u432 ng k\u7871 t th\'e0nh th\u7921 c th\u7875 , ng\u7909 y trang th\'e0nh con ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'e0 tr\u7897 n trong x\'e3 h\u7897 i lo\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\'ec kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e2u d\'e0i, t\'e0 kh\'ed c\u7911 a n\'f3 c\'f3 l\u7869  v\u7851 n \u273 ang hao m\'f2n, v\'ec v\u7853 y n\'f3 m\u7899 i s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t m\u7841 o hi\u7875 m xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i t\u7847 n su\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe xong ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\'f9ng m\'ecnh m\u7897 t c\'e1i, h\u7887 i: "... T\'ecm k\'fd th\u7875 ... ph\u7843 i h\u7841 i nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y sao? H\u417 n n\u7919 a nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i kia t\u7841 i sao l\u7841 i t\u7899 i t\'ecm em?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i t\'e0 thu\u7853 t, n\u7871 u n\'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 k\'fd th\u7875  th\u7921 c th\u7875  tr\u7901 i sinh, ph\u7843 i t\'ecm cho m\'ecnh m\u7897 t k\'fd th\u7875  ph\'f9 h\u7907 p th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i th\u7913  kia m\'e0 n\'f3i c\'e1ch \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i ch\'ednh l\'e0 gom \u273 \u7911  m\'e1u th\u7883 t ch\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7907 p th\'e0nh m\u7897 t c\u417  th\u7875 . V\u7873  ph\u7847 n c\u7853 u..." H\u7891  Tinh chuy\u7875 n h\u432 \u7899 ng sang Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u t\u7915  tr\'ean xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'e1i tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n \u273 ang treo l\'ean theo l\u7901 i c\'f4, l\'fac n\'e0y ch\u7907 t th\u7845 y m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\'f4ng x\'f9 nh\u7887  v\u7875 nh hai c\'e1i tai nh\u7885 n m\'e0u \u273 en chui ra t\u7915  trong chi\u7871 c t\'fai x\'e1ch c\u7905  l\u7899 n c\u7911 a H\u7891  Tinh, "Chiii" k\'eau m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, \'e1nh m\u7855 t to tr\'f2n m\'e0u n\'e2u nha\u803 t c\'f3 ch\'fat t\u7911 i th\'e2n nh\'ecn H\u7891  Tinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh s\u7901  s\u7901  n\'f3, h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 tr\u7845 n an m\u7897 t phen r\u7891 i m\u7899 i nh\'e9t n\'f3 v\'e0o l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 h\u7891  ly \u273 en t\'f4i nu\'f4i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i y\'eau qu\'e1i, nh\u432 ng r\u7845 t c\'f3 linh t\'ednh. T\'f4i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u nu\'f4i n\'f3 l\'fac \u7903  s\u432  m\'f4n, c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7845 n t\'e0, y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u s\u7907  n\'f3, c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\'fap t\'f4i kh\'f4ng \'edt."\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7843 i th\'edch xong c\'f4 m\u7899 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c tr\u7843  l\u7901 i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean. C\'f4 nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\'f3 ch\'fat ch\u7847 n ch\u7915  n\'f3i: "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd t\u7913  x\'fac ph\u7841 m, ch\u7881  l\'e0 h\u7887 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u x\'e1c nh\u7853 n, ch\'ednh c\u7853 u c\'f3 bi\u7871 t hay kh\'f4ng, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u t\'e0 kh\'ed r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em? T\'e0 kh\'ed r\uc0\u7845 t n\u7863 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u c\'f3 t\'e0 kh\'ed r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\'e0 tr\u7901 i sinh \u273 \'e3 c\'f3. Ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7871 u mang theo t\'e0 kh\'ed n\u7863 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y s\u7907  l\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 l\u7879  kh\'ed n\u7863 ng m\'e0 ph\'fac b\'e1o ng\u7855 n, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 tai ho\u7841  b\u7897 c ph\'e1t m\'e0 \u273 o\u7843 n m\u7879 nh. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7899 i t\'e0 kh\'ed kia l\u7841 i r\u7845 t ph\'f9 h\u7907 p, c\u361 ng r\u7845 t hi\u7871 m th\u7845 y, t\'e0 kh\'ed \u273 \'f3 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng h\u7841 i c\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i l\u7841 i ph\'e1t ra t\'e1c d\u7909 ng b\u7843 o v\u7879  c\u7853 u, khi\u7871 n y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n c\u7853 u. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u361 ng b\u7903 i t\'e0 kh\'ed n\'e0y, r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'e3 khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u b\u7883  y\'eau t\'e0 m\u7841 nh ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i, t\'f4i suy \u273 o\'e1n l\u7847 n n\'e0y th\u7913  kia r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\'ednh l\'e0 v\'ec c\'e1i n\'e0y m\'e0 ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \'e1nh m\uc0\u7855 t sinh ra hai ph\u7847 n tr\u7845 n an: "... Kh\'f4ng sai, t\'f4i \u273 o\'e1n kh\'f4ng sai, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i th\u7913  h\'f3a th\'e2n th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, ch\'ednh c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i. L\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i kia, m\u7897 t l\'e0 v\'ec b\u7843 n th\'e2n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 b\u7883  y\'eau t\'e0 l\'e0m h\u7841 i, kh\'e1c v\u7899 i qu\u7927  qu\'e1i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng; th\u7913  hai r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 v\'ec... C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m b\u7883  th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 ch\u7885 n, tr\u7903  th\'e0nh m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n k\'fd th\u7875  tr\u7885 ng y\u7871 u m\'e0 n\'f3 t\'ecm."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y da \u273 \u7847 u run l\'ean t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7907 t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mu\u7889 n nh\u7843 y d\u7921 ng l\'ean!\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'ecnh d\'e1ng c\'e1c b\uc0\u7841 n h\u7885 c \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng ti\u7871 p x\'fac t\u7915 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t l\u432 \u7899 t qua tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, ho\u7863 c vui ho\u7863 c bu\u7891 n, ho\u7863 c gi\u7853 n ho\u7863 c c\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7885 n h\u7885  r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c ai l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, ai l\'e0 y\'eau ma kho\'e1c da ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u run r\u7849 y h\u7887 i c\'f4 g\'e1i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t: "Ch\u7883 , ch\u7883  c\'f3 bi\u7871 t th\u7913  kia r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 ai kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "T\'f4i c\u361 ng v\u7851 n lu\'f4n t\'ecm tung t\'edch th\u7913  kia, c\u361 ng \u273 ang nghi\'ean c\u7913 u bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p di\u7879 t tr\u7915  n\'f3, nh\u432 ng n\'f3 ng\u7909 y trang th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  d\'f9ng m\'f9i c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i xung quanh che gi\u7845 u b\u7843 n th\'e2n, kh\'f4ng d\u7877  t\'ecm. T\'f4i ch\u7881  c\'f3 t\u7921  m\'ecnh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y n\'f3 th\'ec m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t Vi\'ean B\'e1c l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  tin t\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7853 u ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y H\u7891  Tinh \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p, n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7863 ng l\u7869  h\u7865 n \u7903  n\u417 i c\'f4ng c\u7897 ng, c\u7853 u mang nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y c\u7853 u ti\u7871 p x\'fac t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7871 n, t\'f4i s\u7869  \'e2m th\u7847 m quan s\'e1t trong \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 y\'eau v\u7853 t kia hay kh\'f4ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 "... V\'e2ng." Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n m\'ecnh s\u7869  l\u7841 i ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i y\'eau v\u7853 t kia d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t g\'ec, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh th\u7845 y c\u7853 u b\u7897  d\'e1ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng \u273 \u7897 ng l\'f2ng th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7843 m, hu\u7889 ng chi bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c manh m\u7889 i quan tr\u7885 ng t\u7915  ch\u7895  c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t n\'e0y, c\'f4 v\u7895  v\u7895  t\'fai x\'e1ch, \'f4m h\u7891  ly \u273 en nh\u7887  t\u7915  trong t\'fai ra \u273 \u432 a cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Hai ng\'e0y n\'e0y c\u7853 u mang A S\'eanh theo c\u7853 u \u273 i. N\'f3 tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ai l\'e0 y\'eau t\'e0, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u l\u7841 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, \'edt nh\u7845 t A S\'eanh c\'f3 th\u7875  che ch\u7903  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh ma qu\u7927  \u273 \'f3 l\'e0m h\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng am hi\u7875 u c\'e1ch \u7903  chung v\u7899 i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t nh\u7887 , nh\u432 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n h\u7891  ly nh\u7887  n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7845 n t\'e0 v\u7853 t th\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c li\'ean t\u7909 c n\'f3i c\u7843 m \u417 n nh\u7853 n l\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh d\u7863 n d\'f2 m\u7897 t v\'e0i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  cho \u259 n c\u7847 n ch\'fa \'fd c\'e1c lo\u7841 i, l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7893  sung m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "A S\'eanh l\'e0 gi\u7889 ng c\'e1i, c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \'e3i v\u7899 i n\'f3 th\u7853 t t\u7889 t \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng b\u7903 i c\'e2u n\'f3i h\'e0i h\u432 \u7899 c n\'e0y m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tho\'e1ng th\u7843  l\u7887 ng, d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  ch\u7881  b\u7843 o c\u7911 a H\u7891  Tinh thu A S\'eanh v\'e0o trong ba l\'f4 c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, h\u417 i m\u7903  kh\'f3a \u273 \u7875  th\'f4ng kh\'ed cho n\'f3, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i nh\u7899  t\u7899 i vi\u7879 c trao \u273 \u7893 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i H\u7891  Tinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0m xong t\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843 , c\u7853 u suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\u7841 i n\'f3i: "H\u7891  t\u7927 , bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i ch\u7883  c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec kh\'f4ng? Em mu\u7889 n nh\u7901  ch\u7883  nh\'ecn gi\'fap em m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n thi\u7871 t nh\u7845 t \u7903  chung v\u7899 i m\'ecnh th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i nh\u7845 t trong kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y, cho d\'f9 ch\u7881  l\'e0 l\'e0m \u273 i\u7873 u th\u7915 a, d\'f9 sao tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i x\'e1c nh\u7853 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi x\'e1c th\u7921 c gi\u7889 ng Vi\'ean B\'e1c, ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i y\'eau v\u7853 t ng\u7909 y trang th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i kia r\u7891 i m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  y\'ean l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh n\'f3i: "Bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\'f3 vi\u7879 c r\u7891 i. Nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  h\u7865 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 t\u7899 i th\'ec t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  qua th\u7859 ng \u273 \'f3 nh\'ecn th\u7917  xem sao."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e1p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, sau \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n h\u7887 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \u7903  \u273 \'e2u, r\u7845 t nhanh nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7891 i \'e2m c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i \u273 ang \u7903  th\u432  vi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i nh\u7855 n l\u7841 i k\'eau Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  \u273 \'f3 ch\u7901 , n\'f3i m\'ecnh c\'f3 vi\u7879 c mu\u7889 n t\'ecm h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 v\'ec chuy\u7879 n g\'ec m\'e0 ph\u7843 i v\u7897 i v\'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, c\'e1i n\'e0y ki\u7871 m c\u7899  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\u7877 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy t\u432  m\u7897 t l\'e1t, mua m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t t\u7915  ti\u7879 m b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t b\'ean c\u7841 nh qu\'e1n l\u7849 u, \u273 \'f3ng g\'f3i xong x\'e1ch l\'ean, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i c\'f9ng H\u7891  Tinh ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i th\u432  vi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\'e0 H\u7891  Tinh gi\u7843  b\u7897  nh\u432  kh\'f4ng quen bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t \u273 i sau ti\u7871 n v\'e0o trong, H\u7891  Tinh m\u7863 t m\u361 i tr\u7867 , gi\u7843  l\'e0m sinh vi\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec l\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7921 a theo tin nh\u7855 n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7855 n \u273 ang \u7903  l\u7847 u hai th\u432  vi\u7879 n, ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng ch\u7895  b\'ean c\u7841 nh h\u7855 n, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y H\u7891  Tinh gi\u7843  b\u7897  nh\u432  \u273 ang t\'ecm s\'e1ch \u273 i t\u7899 i k\u7879  s\'e1ch ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a ph\'eda sau b\u7885 n h\u7885  hai h\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u l\u7853 t m\u7897 t trang, kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "L\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? T\'ecm t\'f4i g\u7845 p th\u7871  n\'e0y?"\cb1 \
