\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n t\u7899 i r\u7891 i c\u7853 u m\u7899 i s\u7921 c nh\u7853 n ra l\'fd do n\'e0y s\u7913 t s\u7865 o c\u7905  n\'e0o, l\u7897 n x\u7897 n nh\u432  c\u7853 u nh\'f3c ng\'e2y th\u417  theo \u273 u\u7893 i c\'f4 b\'e9 m\'ecnh th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'ean c\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i b\u7893  sung: "... V\u7899 i l\u7841 i c\'f2n mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i h\'f4m nay c\u7853 u v\u7873  \u273 \'e2u ng\u7911 , v\u7873  k\'ed t\'fac hay l\'e0 v\u7873  nh\'e0..."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7881 m n\'f3i: "T\'f4i ng\u7911  \u7903  \u273 \'e2u c\'f3 \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "T\'f4i mu\u7889 n n\'f3i d\'f9 c\u7853 u c\'f3 \u273 i \u273 \'e2u th\'ec mang t\'f4i theo v\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong l\uc0\u417 \u768 i n\'e0y c\u7853 u m\u7899 i b\u7845 t gi\'e1c c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng trong l\'f2ng, m\u7863 c d\'f9 chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng, nh\u432 ng ng\u7897  nh\u7905  v\u7883  H\u7891  t\u7927  kia n\'f3i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7855 n c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
