\cf2 \cb3 Sau khi ng\uc0\u7891 i v\'e0o xe Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'e1o ba l\'f4 xu\u7889 ng \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, h\u7891  ly \u273 en kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n th\'f2 \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  trong ra nh\'ecn c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'e0n nh\u7841 t li\u7871 c qua: "G\'ec \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i vi\u7879 c H\u7891  Tinh c\u7889  \'fd \u273 u\u7893 i l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 i kh\'f4ng cho h\u7855 n d\'ednh v\'e0o chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927  l\'e0m lo\u7841 n n\'e0y, n\'f3i l\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t. Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n g\u7863 p ma \u273 \u7873 u g\u7885 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\u7875  v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, b\'e2y gi\u7901  bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n khi\u7871 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng li\'ean l\u7909 y, v\'ec v\u7853 y thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i b\u7915 a: "D\u7841 o n\'e0y l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 ang theo \u273 u\u7893 i m\u7897 t c\'f4 g\'e1i, g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ph\u7843 i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i n\'ean \u273 em ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly g\u7917 i g\u7855 m cho h\u7855 n, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y ban ng\'e0y h\u7855 n ph\u7843 i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i th\u7921 c t\u7853 p kh\'f4ng ch\u259 m s\'f3c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, th\u7871  n\'ean l\u7841 i \u273 em ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly giao cho t\'f4i. H\'f4m nay m\u7901 i t\'f4i \u259 n c\u417 m ch\u7911  y\u7871 u l\'e0 v\'ec chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, t\'f4i thay h\u7855 n ch\u259 m s\'f3c m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i nay nu\'f4i g\'ec l\'e0m th\'fa c\u432 ng c\u361 ng c\'f3, nu\'f4i ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly tuy r\u7857 ng \'edt, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 qu\'e1 k\u7923  qu\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y l\u7841 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n tr\u432 ng c\u7847 u \'fd ki\u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "... L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c qu\'ean h\u7887 i c\u7853 u, c\'f3 th\u7875  mang ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng?" C\u7853 u nh\u7899  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i c\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c cho h\u7855 n m\u432 \u7907 n \u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  b\u7909 ng, n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng sao, nh\'e0 t\'f4i kh\'f4ng s\u7907  c\'f3 \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t nh\u7887  v\'e0o, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t nh\u7887  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t s\u7907  t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  cho l\'e0 h\u7855 n \u273 ang n\'f3i gi\u7905 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd l\u7901 i h\u259 \u769 n n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tr\uc0\u7903  l\u7841 i nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0m m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u7893  ngay trong ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p cho ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly, qu\u7843  nhi\'ean \u273 \'fang nh\u432  l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i, h\u7855 n \u273 i v\'e0o n\u7845 u c\u417 m ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly li\u7873 n "t\u7915  t\u7915 " ch\u7841 y ra, thay \u273 \u7893 i b\u7897  d\u7841 ng l\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 ng l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t tia ch\u7899 p m\'e0u \u273 en, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u432 \u7901 i ha ha.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i mua \u273 \u7891  \u259 n xong v\u7873  nh\'e0 c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\u259 m gi\u7901 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  trong b\u7871 p sau khi chu\u7849 n b\u7883  xong nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  c\u7847 n chu\u7849 n b\u7883  li\u7873 n ng\u7891 i v\'e0o gh\u7871  \u259 n, l\u7845 y b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean mua ra b\u7887  v\'e0o \u273 \u297 a, c\u7847 m d\u297 a nh\u7887  b\u259 \u768 ng ba\u803 c c\u7855 t t\u7915 ng mi\u7871 ng nh\u7887  b\u7887  v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng, nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u n\u234 \u769 m n\u7871 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7891 i \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n h\u7855 n tr\'f4ng mong nh\'ecn, h\u7887 i: "\u258 n ngon kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i x\u7855 n m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng nh\u7887  \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i b\'ean mi\u7879 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u259 n h\u7871 t m\u7899 i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u th\'edch \u259 n c\'e1i n\'e0y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n d\'f9ng d\u297 a g\u7849 y g\u7849 y b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t, kh\'f4ng kh\'e1ch kh\'ed ch\'fat n\'e0o \u259 n h\u7871 t ch\u7895  c\'f2n l\u7841 i: "C\'e1i n\'e0y t\'f4i c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0m, h\'f4m kh\'e1c l\'e0m cho c\u7853 u \u259 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c." Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1p, th\u7921 c ra b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t tuy r\u7857 ng \u259 n ngon nh\u432 ng n\'f3i chung \u259 n nhi\u7873 u s\u7869  ng\u7845 y, v\u7851 n l\'e0 l\u7849 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m ngon h\u417 n, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n \u259 n bao nhi\'eau, cho d\'f9 \u259 n qu\'e1 no c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\'e1n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u ng\u7841 i n\'f3i ra, n\'f3i ra li\u7873 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u ng\u7845 p ngh\'e9 n\u7891 i l\u7849 u nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi t\u7855 m r\u7917 a xong li\u7873 n b\'f2 l\'ean ch\u7895  thu\u7897 c v\u7873  c\u7853 u tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ng\u7911 , l\'fac Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7855 m r\u7917 a xong \u273 i ra c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng s\u7855 p ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n, m\u432 \u7907 n \'e1nh tr\u259 ng h\'edp m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 a tay nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng s\u7901  l\'ean t\'f3c c\u7853 u, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "Xem nh\u432  c\u7853 u nghe l\u7901 i, kh\'f4ng cho l\'e0 c\'f3 h\u7891  ly c\'e1i b\u7843 o v\u7879  r\u7891 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n l\'e3o c\'f4ng n\u7919 a." Thanh \'e2m h\u7855 n tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p, c\'f2n mang theo \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0n nh\u7841 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i qua, v\'e9n t\'f3c x\'f5a tr\'ean tr\'e1n c\u7853 u, kh\u7869  h\'f4n l\'ean tr\'e1n c\u7853 u. L\u7841 i n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh, k\'e9o ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7919 ng v\'e0ng \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  h\u7915  hai ti\u7871 ng, v\'f9i tr\'ean vai Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng, ng\u7911  say s\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \'eam v\'f4 s\u7921 , ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng nhau l\'e0m t\u7893  trong ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7885 c s\'e1ch, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m laptop kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 ang l\'e0m g\'ec. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh h\u7855 n \'f4m laptop c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ch\u7881 nh s\u7917 a s\u7889  li\u7879 u, tuy r\u7857 ng th\u7847 y h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n t\u7841 m th\u7901 i \u273 i v\u7855 ng, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i g\u7917 i mail b\'e1o c\'e1o c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7883 nh k\'ec cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m qu\'e1 m\u7913 c l\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i d\u7883 ch d\u7883 ch ng\u7891 i c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895 , qu\u7843  th\u7921 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  h\u7885 c tr\'f2 ng\u7891 i c\'f9ng b\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n gi\u7901  c\u417 m hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i \u259 n, n\'ean t\u7855 m n\'ean ng\u7911  \u273 \u7873 u c\'f9ng nhau l\'e0m, l\'e0m vi\u7879 c v\'e0 ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i v\'f4 c\'f9ng \u273 \u7891 ng b\u7897 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'eam khuya, l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nghe th\u7845 y ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng k\'eau y\u7871 u \u7899 t c\u7911 a \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t nh\u7887 , c\u7853 u n\u7857 m t\u7841 i ch\u7895  ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t th\u7853 t k\u7929 , ph\'e1t gi\'e1c h\'ecnh nh\u432  gi\u7889 ng ti\u7871 ng k\'eau c\u7911 a ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly A S\'eanh. H\u7891  ly kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng v\u7899 i ch\'f3 m\'e8o th\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y h\u7891  ly k\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7921 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean "b\u7897 p" m\u7897 t c\'e1i, nh\u7899  t\u7899 i l\u7901 i H\u7891  Tinh \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7845 n t\'e0 li\u7873 n \u273 o\'e1n c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng. C\u7853 u nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang ng\u7911  say b\'ean c\u7841 nh, l\u7863 ng l\u7869  ch\u7881 nh \u273 \u7897  s\'e1ng \u273 \'e8n gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\'ean m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng bi\u7871 n \u273 \u7893 i theo th\u7901 i \u273 \u7841 i, ng\'e0y x\u432 a m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7847 m \u273 u\u7889 c, n\u7871 n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i s\u7869  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y an to\'e0n, v\u7873  sau m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'f9ng \u273 \'e8n pin, \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  th\'ec \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh v\u7853 t c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u7843 m th\u7845 y an to\'e0n nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3 c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  chi\u7871 u s\'e1ng, quan tr\u7885 ng h\u417 n l\'e0 n\'f3 c\'f3 ngh\u297 a c\'f3 th\u7875  li\'ean l\u7841 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  th\u7871  gi\u7899 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i. Con ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7907  nh\u7845 t c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i y\'eau ma tai h\u7885 a, m\'e0 l\'e0 t\u7913  c\u7889  v\'f4 th\'e2n, bi\u7871 t r\'f5 ch\'ednh m\'ecnh th\'e2n \u7903  tuy\u7879 t c\u7843 nh nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o tho\'e1t n\u7841 n, tuy\u7879 t v\u7885 ng kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7913 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n t\u7915  tr\'ean c\u7847 u thang, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n m\'e9p c\u7847 u thang theo ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng nh\'ecn xu\u7889 ng ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i, ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly \u273 ang tr\u7915 ng \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u n\'e2u nha\u803 t v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7847 u thang, n\'f3 nghe th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh, quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\u7841 i ch\u7841 y l\'ean hai b\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t m\u7921 c ng\u259 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean. T\u7913  chi n\'f3 ch\u7889 ng tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, l\'f4ng ph\u7847 n g\'e1y h\u417 i d\u7921 ng l\'ean, th\u7845 p \u273 \u7847 u nghi\'eang v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, b\u7897  d\'e1ng gi\u7889 ng th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c chu\u7849 n b\u7883  c\'f4ng k\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  \u273 \'e8n t\u432 \u7901 ng h\'e0nh lang l\u7847 u hai, l\u7901  m\u7901  chi\u7871 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch trong g\'f3c t\u7889 i l\u7847 u m\u7897 t\'97\'97 ch\'fang \u273 \u7913 ng th\u7859 ng t\u7855 p \u7903  \u273 \'f3, m\u7897 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u361 i, m\u7897 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tai.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y th\u7871  m\'e0 l\u7841 i l\'e0 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7875 u h\u7891  ly nhe nanh, kh\u7869  k\'eau l\'ean b\'e0y ra t\u432  th\u7871  uy hi\u7871 p, hai th\u7913  kia r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, v\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361  t\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t, \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c di chuy\u7875 n v\u7873  ph\'eda l\u7847 u tr\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\uc0\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c lui v\u7873  sau m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, ngo\'e0i d\u7921  li\u7879 u l\'e0 ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly c\u361 ng theo c\u7853 u l\'f9i l\u7841 i m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn ch\uc0\u7857 m ch\u7857 m v\u7853 t nh\u7887  d\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n, trong l\'f2ng t\u7921  nh\u7911  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7913 , ti\u7875 u th\u432  mi nh\'ecn qua r\u7845 t l\u7907 i h\u7841 i, ch\u7911  nh\'e2n mi c\u361 ng khen mi c\'f3 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh c\'f3 th\u7875  h\u7895  tr\u7907 , nh\u432 ng th\u7853 t ra mi ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t con h\u7891  ly ngo\'e0i m\u7841 nh trong y\u7871 u ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t ra v\u7867  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7897 i t\'e2m c\u7853 u quay cu\u7891 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng, nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m hai h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7895  c\u7847 u thang kia, c\u7889  n\'e9n c\u417 n k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 ch\u7841 y, tr\u7889 n v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  kh\'f3a c\u7917 a l\u7841 i r\'fat v\'e0o trong ch\u259 n tr\u7889 n \u7903  b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'e0nh lang c\uc0\u361 ng trong m\u7897 t t\'edch t\u7855 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean s\'e1ng l\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7903  c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i l\'fac \u273 i ra c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 kh\u7869  \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i, \u273 ang m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  ng\u7911  d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\u7917 a nh\'ecn m\'ecnh, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, mang theo m\u7897 t tia \u432 u nh\'e3 v\'e0 thong dong l\'e0m l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i an t\'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e8n tr\u7847 n ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  s\'e1ng r\'f5, sau khi c\u7917 a m\u7903  li\u7873 n tr\'e0n ra ngo\'e0i, chi\u7871 u s\'e1ng h\'e0nh lang l\u417 \u768  m\u417 \u768 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng t\u7841 i m\u7897 t t\'edch t\u7855 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7907  h\'e3i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7847 u thang, hai b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i qu\u7843  nhi\'ean \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u417 i nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "H\u417 n n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  ch\u7841 y ra \u273 \'e2y l\'e0m g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng \'f4m l\u7845 y ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly, b\u7883 a l\'fd do n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec c\u7843 ... ch\u7881  l\'e0 nghe th\u7845 y h\u7891  ly k\'eau, s\u7907  n\'f3 \u273 \'f3i b\u7909 ng b\u7883  b\u7879 nh g\'ec \u273 \'f3." Sau khi nghe H\u7891  Tinh n\'f3i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t kh\'f4ng n\'ean d\'ednh d\'e1ng \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, c\u7853 u li\u7873 n c\u7889  \'fd \u273 \u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\'e1nh xa kh\u7887 i nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y th\u7913  kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i cho h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i thong th\u7843  nh\'ecn c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i m\u7899 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng \'f4m n\'f3, lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t n\'e0y v\u7899 i ch\'f3 m\'e8o b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nhau, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  mang vi khu\u7849 n g\'e2y b\u7879 nh ho\u7863 c k\'fd sinh tr\'f9ng. L\u7841 i n\'f3i nam n\u7919  th\u7909  th\u7909  b\u7845 t th\'e2n, t\'f4i nghe n\'f3i h\u7891  ly \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 linh t\'ednh, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 h\u7891  ly c\'e1i, c\u7853 u \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t l\u7855 m \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t c\'e2u tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f2n c\'f3 \u273 \u7841 o l\'fd, m\u7897 t c\'e2u sau ch\u7881  thu\u7847 n t\'fay l\'e0 n\'f3i linh tinh. Nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nghe l\u7901 i m\'e0 b\u7887  ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 A S\'eanh l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c th\'e0nh th\u7853 t ch\u7841 y xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u, xem b\u7897  d\'e1ng l\'e0 t\u7921  m\'ecnh quay v\u7873  \u7893  r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'e2m th\uc0\u7847 m th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t h\u417 i, v\u7915 a m\u7899 i tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y hai th\u7913  kia \u7903  g\'f3c c\u7847 u thang khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u l\'fac n\'e0y th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\u7921  m\'ecnh xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u \u273 em ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly v\u7873  \u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n lu\'f4n im l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\u7853 u r\'f5 r\'e0ng b\u7883  d\u7885 a qu\'e1 m\u7913 c m\'e0 v\u7851 n c\u7889  n\'e9n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7897  ra ch\'fat \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i, ngo\u7855 c ngo\u7855 c tay v\u7899 i c\u7853 u: "C\'f2n \u273 \u7913 ng ng\u7889 c \u7903  \u273 \u7845 y l\'e0m g\'ec, mau quay l\u7841 i ng\u7911 ."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i theo h\u7855 n v\'e0o c\u7917 a, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n kh\'f3a k\u7929  c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  r\u7891 i m\u7899 i b\'f2 l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng t\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n gi\u432 \u7901 ng. Ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  l\u7841 i l\'e2m v\'e0o trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i, m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u sau c\u7853 u m\u7899 i l\'e9n d\'f2 x\'e9t b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 ng\u7911  l\u7841 i, l\u7863 ng l\u7869 , t\u7921  nh\u7853 n kh\'f4ng ai ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n d\u7883 ch d\u7883 ch v\u7873  ph\'eda ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong b\'f3ng t\uc0\u7889 i, kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u417 i cong l\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u7889 n l\'ean ban c\'f4ng g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho H\u7891  Tinh n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n ph\'e1t sinh \u273 \'eam qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m H\uc0\u7891  Tinh \u7903  \u273 \u7847 u b\'ean kia nghe r\u7845 t m\u7879 t m\u7887 i: "Xem ra v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\u7841 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\u7847 n n\'e0y m\u7897 t l\u7847 n l\u7841 i xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i... Th\u7913  kia qu\u7843  th\u7853 t n\'f4n n\'f3ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7899 i bi\u7871 t th\'ec ra hai ng\'e0y nay H\u7891  Tinh c\u361 ng \u273 ang b\u7853 n r\u7897 n chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, m\u7895 i khi \u273 \'eam \u273 \u7871 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\u7889  g\u7855 ng truy t\'ecm d\u7845 u v\u7871 t y\'eau t\'e0 kia, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng thu ho\u7841 ch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, H\u7891  t\u7927 , v\u7851 n c\'f2n m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c, sau chuy\u7879 n h\'f4m qua ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly li\u7873 n c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m \u7911  r\u361  kh\'f4ng ph\u7845 n ch\u7845 n, s\'e1ng nay em cho \u259 n n\'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u259 n bao nhi\'eau, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 b\u7883  l\'e0m sao?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m nu\'f4i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t, n\'f3i chi l\'e0 nu\'f4i h\u7891  ly, g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nhanh ch\'f3ng tr\u432 ng c\u7847 u \'fd ki\u7871 n ch\u7911  nh\'e2n c\u7911 a n\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh nghe xong r\u7845 t s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t, h\u7887 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7881  nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\'f3i c\'f4 s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean h\u417 n m\u7897 t gi\u7901  sau c\'f4 \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i d\u7889 i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0 c\'f4 g\'e1i l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 ang theo \u273 u\u7893 i g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly g\u7917 i nu\'f4i, xong li\u7873 n \'f4m A S\'eanh \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh \u273 au l\'f2ng \'f4m v\u7853 t nh\u7887  v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, vu\u7889 t vu\u7889 t tai c\u7911 a n\'f3. Ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly d\u7921 a \u7903  trong ng\u7921 c c\'f4 k\'eau nh\u7887  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\u7885  c\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 \'f4m A S\'eanh nh\'ecn nhi\uc0\u7873 u l\u7847 n, th\u7903  d\'e0i ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i: "May m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7841 i, ch\u7881  l\'e0 b\u7883  t\'e0 kh\'ed *ph\u7843 n xung."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (ph\uc0\u7843 n xung: t\'e1c \u273 \u7897 ng d\u7897 i ng\u432 \u7907 c tr\u7903  l\u7841 i)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7883  t\'e0 kh\'ed ph\u7843 n xung?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean n\'f3i. Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i n\'f3i ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7845 n t\'e0 \u432 ? V\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  t\'e0 kh\'ed ph\u7843 n xung?\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "A S\'eanh \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i th\u7913  kia m\u7851 n c\u7843 m h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i con ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fang ta, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra t\'e0 kh\'ed n\'f3 s\u7869  v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Nh\'ecn n\'f3 th\u7871  n\'e0y... H\u7859 n l\'e0 hai ng\'e0y nay \u7903  ch\u7895  c\u7853 u ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i th\u7913  t\'e0 kh\'ed r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7871  n\'e0y. T\'f4i kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i th\u7913  kia t\'e0 kh\'ed kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  l\u7841 i l\u7907 i h\u7841 i nh\u432  th\u7871 , ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  n\'f3 h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh o\'e1n qu\u7927  v\u7853 y m\'e0 c\u361 ng mang theo t\'e0 kh\'ed n\u7863 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  \u273 \u7871 n A S\'eanh."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\'f4i ph\u7843 i mang A S\'eanh v\u7873  tu d\u432 \u7905 ng, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  n\'f3 ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y n\u7919 a, t\u7921  c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat." H\u7891  Tinh d\u7863 n d\'f2.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'f2ng t\uc0\u7921  nh\u7911  kh\'f4ng sao, th\u7845 y ti\u7875 u gia h\u7887 a n\'e0y \u7903  ch\u7895  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n c\u7853 u c\u361 ng r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e0nh, hu\u7889 ng chi n\'f3i th\u7853 t c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly n\'e0y v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng nh\u432  b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\u7853 u nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7887 i th\u259 m H\u7891  Tinh: "H\u7891  t\u7927 , b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng em r\'fat cu\u7897 c l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p g\'ec? Ch\u7883  n\'f3i c\u7853 u \u7845 y l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\u432 ng h\'ecnh nh\u432  m\u7895 i l\u7847 n c\u7853 u ta v\u7915 a xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n nh\u7919 ng ma qu\u7927  \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "T\'f4i \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 n\u7919 a, con ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i sinh linh r\u7845 t ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ed v\u7853 n th\u7883 nh, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i *b\'e1t t\u7921  n\u7863 ng, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7915  nh\u7887  c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\u7855 c v\u7841 n t\'e0, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Tr\u7901 i v\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i nghi\'ean c\u7913 u ch\'ednh l\'e0 '\u272 \u7841 o', t\'f4i nghi\'ean c\u7913 u thu\u7853 t h\'e0ng ma tr\u7915  t\'e0 t\u7915  nh\u7887 , t\u7853 p luy\u7879 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 'Ph\'e1p' . V\u432 \u7907 t qu\'e1 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  chuy\'ean m\'f4n, t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ch\'ednh x\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
