\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7921 a theo l\u7901 i H\u7891  Tinh n\'f3i, th\u7913  kia ph\u7843 i h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t \'edt nh\u7845 t ch\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\'e0 b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n s\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i, th\u7913  kia s\u7907  l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t t\u7899 i m\'ecnh. Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 kh\'f4ng lo s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  b\u7843 y tu\u7847 n n\'e0y l\'fac \u273 i ch\u417 i b\'f3ng r\u7893  Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i tr\u432 \u7899 c v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng v\u7873  \u259 n c\u417 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, t\'ecm \u273 \u7841 i m\u7897 t c\u7899  m\u7901 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u quen bi\u7871 t th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f9ng ch\u417 i b\'f3ng sau khi ch\u417 i xong th\'ec ra ngo\'e0i c\u7893 ng t\'e2y tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c \u259 n \u273 \u7891  n\u432 \u7899 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh v\u7899 i s\u432  \u273 \u7879  c\u7911 a c\'f4 an v\u7883  t\u7841 i m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c b\'e0n kh\'e1c, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\u7863 ng l\u7869  \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 m\u7897 t b\'e0n ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 S\uc0\u432  \u273 \u7879  c\u7911 a c\'f4 ch\'ednh l\'e0 b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7845 p hai kia c\u7911 a l\'e3o Vi\'ean, b\u7903 i v\'ec nghe n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A l\u7847 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n n\'ean c\u7889  \'fd ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i gi\'fap, l\u7841 i b\u7883  H\u7891  Tinh d\u7863 n d\'f2 kh\'f4ng n\'ean m\u7897 t m\'ecnh h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng, c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i b\'e1o cho c\'f4, tr\'e1nh cho h\u7855 n gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  kh\'f4ng th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n th\'e2m \u273 \u7897 c c\u7911 a y\'eau t\'e0 kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tan cu\uc0\u7897 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'eau m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7903  v\u7873 , b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u7903  l\u7841 i t\'ednh ti\u7873 n, h\u7907 p l\u7841 i v\u7899 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i H\u7891  Tinh h\u7887 i: "H\u7891  t\u7927 , th\u7871  n\'e0o r\u7891 i? Ch\u7883  c\'f3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n g\'ec kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac h\uc0\u7887 i nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i trong l\'f2ng l\'e0 t\u432  v\u7883  g\'ec, hy v\u7885 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  mau ch\'f3ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c y\'eau ma kho\'e1c da ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \u273 \u7875  tr\'e1nh c\'f3 th\'eam ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i, l\u7841 i s\u7907  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  n\'f3i ra r\u7857 ng b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\'e0 v\u7853 t h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat th\uc0\u7845 t v\u7885 ng, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t h\u417 i, \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883 : "H\u7891  t\u7927 , th\u7913  hai ch\u7883  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 p em nh\'ecn th\u7917  xem, c\u361 ng c\'f3 kha\u777  n\u259 ng th\u7913  kia xen l\u7851 n trong \u273 \'e1m b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\'f9ng l\u7899 p v\u7899 i em."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u258 n \u273 \u7891  n\u432 \u7899 ng xong th\'ec \u273 \'e3 ch\'edn gi\u7901 , H\u7891  Tinh lo l\u7855 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, n\'f3i v\u7899 i s\u432  \u273 \u7879  c\'f9ng nhau \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 a v\u7873  ch\u7895  \u7903  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, d\'f9 sao c\u7853 u r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7909 c ti\'eau k\u7871  ti\u7871 p c\u7911 a th\u7913  kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7845 t ti\u7871 c m\u7841 ng, lo\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng gi\u7843  v\u7901  kh\'e1ch kh\'ed, kh\'f4ng t\u7915  ch\u7889 i m\'e0 l\'ean xe H\u7891  Tinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean xe n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n phi\u7871 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u7903  h\'e0ng sau, nh\u7899  t\u7899 i ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly: "H\u7891  t\u7927 , A S\'eanh th\u7871  n\'e0o r\u7891 i? \u272 \'e3 kh\'e1 h\u417 n ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'e1 h\uc0\u417 n nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i." H\u7891  Tinh \u273 \'e1p, "N\'f3 m\u7873 m n\u7855 n r\u7855 n bu\'f4ng, b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng r\u7845 t nh\u7841 y b\'e9n, th\u7845 y t\'e0 v\u7853 t c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\u7843 n xung m\'ecnh t\u7921  nhi\'ean s\u7869  bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i n\'e9 tr\'e1nh, kh\'f4ng c\u7913 ng r\u7855 n ti\u7871 n l\'ean \'e1p s\'e1t, v\'ec v\u7853 y an d\u432 \u7905 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng sao n\u7919 a."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (ph\uc0\u7843 n xung: t\'e1c \u273 \u7897 ng d\u7897 i ng\u432 \u7907 c tr\u7903  l\u7841 i)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i b\u7897  d\u7841 ng ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly \u273 \'eam h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 l\'f9i l\u7841 i tr\u7889 n theo m\'ecnh, trong l\'f2ng t\u7921  nh\u7911  \u273 i\u7873 u n\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \'fang. Thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng l\u7841 i n\'f3i: "H\u7891  t\u7927 , em th\u7845 y ch\u7883  r\u7845 t quan t\'e2m ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly kia, ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 v\u7915 a nghe n\'f3i n\'f3 h\'ecnh nh\u432  b\u7883  b\u7879 nh \u273 \'e3 nhanh ch\'f3ng ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 , " H\u7891  Tinh v\u7915 a l\'e1i xe v\u7915 a n\'f3i, "M\u7865  c\u7911 a n\'f3 \u273 \'e3 c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng t\'f4i, t\'f4i ch\u259 m s\'f3c n\'f3 l\'e0 l\u7869  \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7865  c\u7911 a n\'f3? Th\u7871  ch\u7859 ng ph\u7843 i c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t con h\u7891  ly \u432 ? Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe v\u7853 y h\u7871 t s\u7913 c t\'f2 m\'f2, th\u7853 m ch\'ed h\u417 i r\u432 \u7899 n ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean nghi\'eang v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh th\u7845 y c\u7853 u h\u7913 ng th\'fa, d\u7913 t kho\'e1t m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng di\u7877 n gi\u7843 i: "N\'f3 v\'e0 nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n t\'f4i t\u7915 ng tr\u7843 i qua c\'f3 quan h\u7879 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n t\'f4i sinh ra t\u7841 i m\u7897 t th\'f4n t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i l\u7841 c h\u7853 u, cha m\u7865  trong nh\'e0 tr\u7885 ng nam khinh n\u7919 . N\u259 m \u7845 y t\'f4i n\u259 m tu\u7893 i em trai t\'f4i ba tu\u7893 i, b\u7883  ch\u7891 n c\u7855 n. Trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t d\'e2n gian, ch\u7891 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\'e0 lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i y\'eau d\u7883 , ch\u7895  ch\'fang t\'f4i n\'f3i tr\u7867  con b\u7883  ch\u7891 n c\u7855 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  *\u273 \u7841 i ti\'ean b\u7855 t \u273 i r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng c\u7913 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (\uc0\u272 \u7841 i ti\'ean: m\u7897 t c\'e1ch g\u7885 i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t th\'e0nh tinh c\u7911 a d\'e2n gian Trung Qu\u7889 c)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u273 \'f3 s\u432  ph\u7909  t\'f4i \u273 i ngang qua, \'f4ng \u7845 y n\'f3i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7913 u t\'ednh m\u7841 ng em trai t\'f4i, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u c\u432 \u769 u th\'ec nh\'e0 t\'f4i s\u7869  thi\u7871 u n\u7907  \'f4ng m\u7897 t \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7879  *truy\u7873 n y b\'e1t, ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7875  em trai t\'f4i c\'f9ng \'f4ng r\u7901 i \u273 i h\u7885 c thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p. Cha m\u7865  t\'f4i l\'fac \u7845 y v\'ec c\u7913 u t\'ednh m\u7841 ng em t\'f4i n\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, nh\u432 ng ch\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n khi s\u432  ph\u7909  th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\u7913 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c em t\'f4i v\u7873  r\u7891 i th\'ec l\u7841 i \u273 \u7893 i \'fd, th\u432 \u417 ng ti\u7871 c con trai \u273 \u7897 c nh\u7845 t, v\'ec v\u7853 y \u273 \u7849 y t\'f4i ra, \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i \u273 i theo s\u432  ph\u7909  t\'f4i."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 ( Truy\uc0\u7873 n y b\'e1t: ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7885 c tr\'f2 h\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7871 t s\u7903  h\u7885 c ch\'e2n ch\'ednh c\u7911 a th\u7847 y.)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 "S\uc0\u432  ph\u7909  t\'f4i l\'e0 m\u7897 t l\'e3o thu\u7853 t s\u297  v\'e2n du b\u7889 n ph\u432 \u417 ng, b\u7903 i v\'ec khi \u273 \'f3 t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7899 n \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n h\u7841 n ch\u7871  n\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\u7847 n h\'e0n. Nh\u432 ng t\'f4i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng th\u7853 t ra c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7893  h\u417 n l\'fac \u7903  nh\'e0 bao nhi\'eau, c\'f2n t\u7921  do h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u, t\'f4i theo s\u432  ph\u7909  \u273 i t\u7913  ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f2n hi\u7875 u bi\u7871 t th\'eam kh\'f4ng \'edt. Cho \u273 \u7871 n khi m\u432 \u7901 i hai m\u432 \u7901 i ba tu\u7893 i, c\'f3 m\u7897 t l\u7847 n t\'f4i l\'ean n\'fai h\'e1i rau d\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng c\u7849 n th\u7853 n b\u7883  r\u7855 n \u273 \u7897 c c\u7855 n, l\'fac \u7845 y c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t c\u7913 ng, t\'ea d\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch n\u7893 i. Khi \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i m\u7863 c d\'f9 c\'f2n nh\u7887  nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  m\u7845 t m\u7841 ng, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'e1c. L\'fac \u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t h\u7891  ly c\'e1i m\'e0u \u273 en xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, t\'f4i th\u7845 y b\u7909 ng n\'f3 b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i ra r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u m\'e1u. N\'f3 t\u7915  t\u7915  ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n t\'f4i, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean qu\u7923  xu\u7889 ng c\u7855 n l\'ean mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a t\'f4i h\'fat h\u7871 t m\'e1u \u273 \u7897 c ra, sau \u273 \'f3 ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean mi\u7879 ng t\'f4i cho t\'f4i u\u7889 ng m\'e1u v\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t c\u7911 a n\'f3, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o ph\u7843 n kh\'e1ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a t\'f4i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'e1c \'fd, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'e0 \u273 ang c\u7913 u t\'f4i, n\'ean \u273 \u7873 u nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7901 i gian d\u7847 n qua t\'f4i t\u7915  t\u7915  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'e2n th\u7875  kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c tri gi\'e1c, h\u7891  ly kia th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u. M\u7897 t l\'e1t sau n\'f3 l\u7841 i ng\u7853 m trong mi\u7879 ng m\u7897 t con h\u7891  ly con \u273 i t\u7899 i \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean vai t\'f4i, \u273 \u7853 p t\'f4i kh\u7869  k\'eau hai ti\u7871 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\u7903  n\u7919 a. Sau khi ch\'f4n c\u7845 t n\'f3 xong t\'f4i mang ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7863 p s\u432  ph\u7909 , k\u7875  l\u7841 i s\u7921  t\'ecnh cho \'f4ng nghe, s\u432  ph\u7909  n\'f3i con h\u7891  ly \u273 \'f3 bi\u7871 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng, t\'ednh m\u7841 ng kh\'f4ng k\'e9o d\'e0i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u n\u7919 a cho n\'ean m\u7899 i c\u7913 u t\'f4i m\u7897 t m\u7841 ng r\u7891 i g\u7917 i g\u7855 m cho t\'f4i. M\'e1u n\'f3 cho t\'f4i \u259 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\'e1u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, h\u7859 n l\'e0 tinh huy\u7871 t c\u7911 a n\'f3, h\u7891  ly kia v\u7851 n ch\u432 a th\u7875  t\'ednh l\'e0 y\'eau qu\'e1i, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat linh t\'ednh v\'e0 \u273 \u7841 o h\u7841 nh, n\'f3 ch\u7885 n tr\'fang t\'f4i c\u361 ng l\'e0 v\'ec nh\'ecn ra t\'f4i l\'fac \u7845 y tu\u7893 i c\'f2n nh\u7887 , kh\'ed t\u7913 c thu\u7847 n khi\u7871 t ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n \'e1c, h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i tu t\u7853 p thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p, th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  coi tr\u7885 ng nh\'e2n duy\'ean qu\u7843  b\'e1o, l\'fac \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i d\'e1m giao \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  cho t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  l\'e0 v\'ec \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tinh huy\u7871 t c\u7911 a h\u7891  ly, sau l\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i tu t\u7853 p thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p ti\u7871 n b\u7897  c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng nhanh, th\u7853 m ch\'ed r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 v\u432 \u7907 t qua s\u432  ph\u7909 . Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i h\u7885  H\u7891 , nh\u432 ng t\'f4i ngh\u297  cha m\u7865  t\'f4i m\u7863 c d\'f9 cho t\'f4i sinh m\u7879 nh, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i v\u7913 t b\u7887  t\'f4i, nh\'e2n duy\'ean c\u7911 a t\'f4i v\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng li\u7873 n c\u7855 t \u273 \u7913 t; h\u7891  ly l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 c\u7913 u t\'f4i m\u7897 t m\u7841 ng, cho t\'f4i tinh huy\u7871 t, ch\u7859 ng b\u7857 ng t\'f4i s\u7917 a h\u7885  H\u7891  \u273 i. Sau \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i li\u7873 n s\u7917 a th\'e0nh h\u7885  H\u7891 , \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c kia h\u7885  g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 n\'f3i nh\uc0\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i nghe \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7853 p th\u7847 n. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i H\u7891  Tinh c\'f2n t\u7915 ng tr\u7843 i qua nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n xem nh\u432  m\u7897 t c\'e2u chuy\u7879 n, \u273 i\u7873 m nhi\'ean nh\u432  kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i l\u7841 i th\'eam v\'e0i ph\u7847 n kh\'e2m ph\u7909 c v\'e0 t\'edn nhi\u7879 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7845 p hai c\u7911 a l\'e3o Vi\'ean ng\u7891 i \u7903  gh\u7871  l\'e1i ph\u7909 , h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m nghe n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n c\u361  c\u7911 a s\u432  t\u7927 , sau khi nghe xong b\u7893  sung: "\u272 \'fang \u273 \u226 \u769 y, s\u432  ph\u7909  t\'f4i v\'e0 s\u432  t\u7927  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia s\u7889 ng r\u7845 t kham kh\u7893 . V\u7873  sau b\u7855 t k\u7883 p t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n kinh t\u7871  nhanh ch\'f3ng c\u7911 a \u273 \u7845 t n\u432 \u7899 c, t\'ecnh h\'ecnh b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng s\u7843 n t\u7889 t, s\u432  ph\u7909  n\'f3i m\'f2 g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, d\u7921 a v\'e0o vi\u7879 c xem phong th\u7911 y cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta m\u7899 i tr\u7903  th\'e0nh \u273 \u7841 i s\u432  ki\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7873 n an \u7893 n cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng, \u273 \u432 a s\u432  t\u7927  \u273 i h\u7885 c l\'ean cao."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7915 ng c\'f3 n\'f3i linh tinh," H\u7891  Tinh m\u7855 ng, "C\'e1i g\'ec g\u7885 i l\'e0 n\'f3i m\'f2 g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em kh\'f4ng n\'f3i sai m\'e0," b\uc0\u7841 n h\u7885 c l\'e3o Vi\'ean n\'f3i, "S\u432  ph\u7909  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i chuy\'ean m\'f4n nghi\'ean c\u7913 u tr\u7915  ma tr\u7915  t\'e0 sao, xem t\u432 \u7899 ng xem phong th\u7911 y s\u432  ph\u7909  c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u m\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, xem ra l\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o ph\u7843 n b\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7841 n h\u7885 c l\'e3o Vi\'ean l\u7841 i nhanh ch\'f3ng n\u7883 nh n\'f3i: "Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 s\u432  t\u7927  t\'f4i \u273 \'e1ng tin c\u7853 y h\u417 n s\u432  ph\u7909  nhi\u7873 u, ch\u7883  \u7845 y th\u7871  m\'e0 th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7901 i \u273 i ph\'e1 nh\u7919 ng v\u7909  \'e1n h\u7895 n t\u7841 p nhi\u7873 u nghi v\u7845 n kh\'f3 x\u7917  l\'fd m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng xa, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i di \u273 \u7897 ng ra nh\'ecn, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 m\u432 \u7901 i r\u432 \u7905 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh d\u7863 n d\'f2: "Sau khi tr\u7901 i t\u7889 i \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, t\u7853 n l\u7921 c \u7903  trong nh\'e0, kh\'f3a k\u7929  c\u7917 a s\u7893 . D\u7921 a theo l\u7901 i d\'e2n gian th\u432 \u7901 ng n\'f3i, m\u7895 i ng\'f4i nh\'e0 \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 linh h\u7891 n c\u7911 a n\'f3, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kh\'f4ng m\u7901 i m\'e0 t\u7899 i mu\u7889 n v\'e0o trong nh\'e0 h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y. N\u7871 u c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec ph\u7843 i nhanh ch\'f3ng li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u x\'e1c nh\u7853 n, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i H\u7891  Tinh nh\'ecn c\u7853 u c\u7847 m ch\'eca kho\'e1 m\u7903  c\u7917 a \u273 i v\'e0o \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i r\u7891 i m\u7899 i l\'e1i xe r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec Tr\'ec Di\'ean lu\'f4n \u7903  trong nh\'e0, kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 hai ng\'e0y sau l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\u7873 n c\u7853 u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t b\u7897  ch\'eca kho\'e1. L\'fac m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n ng\u7841 i c\u7847 m, v\u7873  sau ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 c\u7917 a r\u7897 ng, v\u7851 n l\'e0 m\'ecnh c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\u7897  ch\'eca kho\'e1 s\u7869  thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n h\u417 n, b\u7899 t cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i ch\u7841 y lui l\'ean l\u7847 u xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u lo l\u7855 ng m\u7903  c\u7917 a cho m\'ecnh, nh\u432  h\'f4m nay b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\u7873  tr\u7877  th\u7871  n\'e0y m\'e0 h\u7855 n v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7907 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o nh\'e0, m\uc0\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7863 t d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch l\u7853 p t\u7913 c s\'e1ng l\'ean, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7853 y m\'e0 \u273 ang an v\u7883  \u7903  tr\'ean s\'f4 pha qu\u7847 n \'e1o ch\u7881 nh t\u7873  ch\u7901  c\u7853 u. Nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u r\u7891 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i kh\'e9p quy\u7875 n s\'e1ch tr\'ean tay l\u7841 i, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i: "V\u7873  r\u7891 i \'e0? L\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 mu\u7897 n th\u7871  ? \u272 i v\u7873  b\u7857 ng g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i cho h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927  n\u7885 , \'fap \'fap m\u7903  m\u7903  n\'f3i: "M\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng nhau \u259 n \u273 \u7891  n\u432 \u7899 ng m\'e0, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i tr\u7877 . L\'e3o Vi\'ean v\u7899 i c\'f4 b\u7841 n h\u7855 n \u273 ang theo \u273 u\u7893 i \u273 \u432 a t\'f4i v\u7873 ." C\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c b\u7883 a chuy\u7879 n th\u7871  n\'e0y ch\'ednh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7855 p tin l\'e3o Vi\'ean th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 ang theo \u273 u\u7893 i H\u7891  Tinh r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y c\u7853 u l\u7841 i nhanh ch\'f3ng b\u7893  sung: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\'f4i nghe n\'f3i d\u7841 o n\'e0y kh\'f4ng an to\'e0n l\u7855 m, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'ean \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean v\u7873  tr\u7877 . C\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'f5 c\u7917 a th\'ec kh\'f4ng n\'ean t\'f9y ti\u7879 n m\u7903 , d\'f9 l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fang ta quen g\'f5 c\u7917 a l\'fac qu\'e1 mu\u7897 n th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ngh\u297  n\u7871 u th\u7913  kia \u273 \'e3 ng\u7909 y trang th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n tr\'e0 tr\u7897 n gi\u7919 a b\u7885 n h\u7885 , v\u7853 y c\u361 ng r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i quen bi\u7871 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, m\u432 \u7907 n th\'e2n ph\u7853 n ng\u432 \u7901 i quen t\u7899 i c\u7917 a h\'e0nh hung c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng d\u7863 n d\'f2 m\'ecnh, \'e1nh m\u7855 t h\u417 i cong l\'ean, \u273 \'e1p: "\u272 \'e3 bi\u7871 t, t\'f4i hi\u7875 u m\'e0, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean cho ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c c\u417  h\u7897 i l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i xong \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, bu\'f4ng s\'e1ch, v\u432 \u417 n tay v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 i n\'e0o, th\u7901 i gian kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7899 m, quay v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, ngoan ngo\'e3n \u273 i theo h\u7855 n l\'ean l\u7847 u tr\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'eam \u273 \'e3 khuya, h\'f4m nay tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7847 y m\'e2y, \'e1nh tr\u259 ng c\u361 ng l\u7863 ng l\u7869  \u7849 n \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh tr\uc0\u259 ng \u7843 m \u273 \u7841 m, trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7859 ng l\u7863 ng m\u7903  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang ng\u7911  say s\u432 a v\'f9i \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh h\u7855 n, tr\u7903  m\'ecnh k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng ng\u7853 m c\u7855 n l\u7895  tai Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i... c\'f3 ph\u7843 i v\u7851 n r\u7845 t lo l\u7855 ng cho l\'e3o c\'f4ng kh\'f4ng..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng n\'f3i mang theo \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p, c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7845 y ph\u7847 n say l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i m\'ea ho\u7863 c ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1ng ti\u7871 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai nghe th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\'ean tai c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7885 c gh\u7865 o qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u m\u7897 ng \u273 \u7865 p, v\u7895  c\'e1i b\u7897 p l\'ean c\u7857 m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
