\cf2 \cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  hai Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t m\'ecnh chen ch\'fac l\'ean t\'e0u \u273 i\u7879 n ng\u7847 m tr\u7903  v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i h\u7885 c, b\u7903 i v\'ec l\'e0 ban ng\'e0y v\u7843  l\u7841 i xung quanh ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i n\'ean c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 s\u7907 , th\u7913  kia m\u7845 y l\u7847 n ra tay h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 khi \u273 \'eam xu\u7889 ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a th\u432 \u7901 ng sau m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh v\'e0 b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7911 a l\'e3o Vi\'ean hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'fang h\u7865 n \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 p c\u7853 u xem m\u7897 t v\'f2ng, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ai kh\u7843  nghi hay b\u7845 t k\'ec \u273 i\u7873 u g\'ec kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 i nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i kh\'e1c trong tr\u432 \u7901 ng t\'ecm manh m\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\uc0\u7899 p, D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh v\u7851 n nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, h\u7855 n nh\'ecn xung quanh m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, tr\'eau gh\u7865 o n\'f3i: "N\'e8, Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, sao ti\u7875 u m\u7929  nh\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n h\u7885 c nh\u7901  khoa ch\'fang ta, l\'f2ng \u273 \u7847 y \u7849 n \'fd kia hai bu\u7893 i r\u7891 i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kho\uc0\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y li\'ean t\u7909 c b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  qu\u7845 n th\'e2n, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i nghe n\'f3i l\'e0 do y\'eau t\'e0 qu\u7845 y ph\'e1, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y b\u7853 n r\u7897 n b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng m\'ecnh \u7889 c c\'f2n kh\'f4ng mang n\u7893 i m\'ecnh \u7889 c, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\'e2u kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  n\u7893 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y. C\u7853 u nghe D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh h\u7887 i v\u7853 y m\u7899 i nh\u7899  ra C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, c\u361 ng ch\u7881  t\'f9y ti\u7879 n qua loa n\'f3i: "\u7914 , ch\u7855 c th\u7845 y ch\'e1n n\'ean kh\'f4ng t\u7899 i n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u \u273 ang gi\u7843  b\u7897  \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7855 n hay l\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u phong t\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Sau khi tan h\uc0\u7885 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c \u273 i b\u7855 t t\'e0u \u273 i\u7879 n ng\u7847 m, D\u432 \u417 ng Thanh mu\u7889 n r\u7911  c\u7853 u c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i \u259 n li\u7873 n b\u7883  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921  c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t: "\u272 \u7875  l\u7847 n sau \u273 i, b\u7841 n t\'f4i l\'e0m c\u417 m \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\u7901  t\'f4i v\u7873  \u259 n r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Thanh nh\'ecn b\'f3ng c\u7853 u b\u432 \u7899 c nhanh r\u7901 i \u273 i, trong l\'f2ng t\u7921  nh\u7911  ai kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t kh\'e9o l\u7841 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\'e0 v\u7907  c\u7853 u \u7903  nh\'e0 n\u7845 u c\u417 m \u273 ang ch\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7873  \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a n\'e0y ng\u432 \u7901 i trong t\'e0u \u273 i\u7879 n ng\u7847 m \'edt h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i l\'fac s\'e1ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ra kh\u7887 i t\'e0u \u273 ang \u273 \'fat tay v\'e0o t\'fai v\u7897 i v\'e3 \u273 i v\u7873  nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, l\u7841 i nghe th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t thanh \'e2m quen thu\u7897 c g\u7885 i c\u7853 u: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean! Tr\'ec Di\'ean!"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n l\u7841 i l\'e0 ch\'fa th\'edm. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ch\'e0o h\u7887 i: "Ch\'fa, th\'edm." N\u417 i \u273 \'e2y v\u7889 n g\u7847 n nh\'e0 ch\'fa, g\u7863 p ch\'fa th\'edm c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec l\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'edm tr\'e1ch c\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 i th\u259 m m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7899  t\u7899 i l\u7901 i n\'f3i d\u7889 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, ho khan m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i: "Nh\'f3m ch\'e1u c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng \u7903  g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y, c\u7853 u \u7845 y \u273 em m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n t\u432  li\u7879 u quan tr\u7885 ng v\u7873  nh\'e0, b\'e2y gi\u7901  th\u7847 y gi\'e1o \u273 ang c\u7847 n ph\u7847 n t\'e0i li\u7879 u \u273 \'f3 n\'ean k\'eau ch\'e1u \u273 i l\u7845 y \u7841 ." C\u7853 u lu\'f4n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c sau khi g\u7863 p qu\u7927  r\u7891 i nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng n\'f3i, b\u7843 n th\'e2n n\'f3i d\u7889 i ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u, n\u259 ng l\u7921 c thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng b\u7883 a chuy\u7879 n c\u361 ng c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa th\'edm nh\'ecn \uc0\u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891 , \u273 \'fang l\'e0 gi\u7901  c\u417 m tr\u432 a, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh mu\u7889 n k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\u7873  nh\'e0 \u259 n c\u417 m. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m c\u417 m xong \u273 ang ch\u7901  \u7903  nh\'e0, li\u7873 n l\u7845 y vi\u7879 c \u273 ang ph\u7843 i l\u7845 y t\u432  li\u7879 u g\u7845 p l\'e0m l\'fd do kh\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915 . Nh\u432 ng ch\'fa th\'edm n\u259 m l\u7847 n b\u7843 y l\u432 \u7907 t nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh m\u7901 i, h\'f4m nay l\u7841 i \u273 \'fang l\'fac g\u7863 p tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, t\u7915  ch\u7889 i n\u7919 a c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u7893 n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng tr\u432 a mai nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 a h\'f4m sau sau khi \u273 i ra t\u7915  nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i si\'eau th\u7883  mua m\u7897 t \'edt b\'e1nh v\'e0 tr\'e0, mang \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ch\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7889 n n\u259 m kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y nh\'e0 ch\'fa, m\u7885 i th\u7913  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng thay \u273 \u7893 i nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn nh\'ecn c\u7847 u thang th\'f4ng l\'ean l\u7847 u tr\'ean, nh\u7899  t\u7899 i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  v\'e0 ph\'f2ng Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 m\'ecnh t\u7915 ng \u7903 , v\u7851 n c\'f3 n\u7895 i s\u7907  kh\'f4ng kh\u7855 c ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7893 i l\'ean trong l\'f2ng. Th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng kh\u7855 c ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a nh\u7899  l\u7841 i n\u7909  h\'f4n mang theo c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh r\u417 i \u7903  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh, t\u7915 ng c\'e1i vu\u7889 t ve \'f4m \u7845 p c\'f9ng v\u7899 i ti\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\u7889 c c\u7911 a th\u7913  kia l\'fac \'e1p \u7903  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh \'f4m m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\'fd \uc0\u7913 c cho t\u7899 i nay v\u7851 n lu\'f4n t\u7853 n l\u7921 c qu\'ean \u273 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7911 y tri\u7873 u d\'e2ng l\'ean, l\u7841 i v\u7851 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng nh\u432  h\'f4m qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7923  d\u7883  ch\'ednh l\'e0, l\u7847 n n\'e0y l\'fac nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n, ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t h\u417 n l\'e0 v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\'eam ch\'fat c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\u7845 t quen, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t quen thu\u7897 c h\u417 i th\u7903  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o v\'e0 nh\u7919 ng \u273 \u7909 ng ch\u7841 m kia...\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  th\u7921 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  k\'fd \u7913 c ki\u7871 p tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  \'fd ngh\u297  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'e0m cho s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c run l\'ean, kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng n\u7871 u cu\u7897 c \u273 \u7901 i m\'ecnh qu\u7843  th\u7853 t v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\u7883  qu\u7927  qu\u7845 n nh\u432  th\u7871  s\u7869  l\'e0 nh\'e2n sinh nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u7891  xu\u7889 ng, h\u7887 i th\u259 m l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t ba v\u7883  tr\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7889 i. Em h\u7885  hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  \u273 ang h\u7885 c \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c \u7903  v\'f9ng kh\'e1c, v\'ec v\u7853 y trong nh\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f3 ba ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fa th\'edm v\'e0 b\'e0 tr\u7867 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 tr\uc0\u7867  hai n\u259 m qua th\u7883  l\u7921 c c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7847 u \'f3c v\u7851 n r\u7845 t minh m\u7851 n, b\'e0 v\u7883 n c\'e1nh tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean quan s\'e1t c\u7853 u h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "L\u7841 i l\u7899 n l\'ean r\u7891 i, l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c g\u7863 p con th\u7853 t gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u7881  m\u7899 i h\'f4m qua, b\'e0 \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra r\u7891 i. B\u7885 n nh\u7887  \'e0, \u273 \u7873 u l\u7899 n nhanh nh\u432  th\u7893 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe v\uc0\u7853 y c\u432 \u7901 i th\u7847 m, b\u7909 ng n\'f3i m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 l\u7899 n th\u7871  n\'e0y r\u7891 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i con n\'edt ba tu\u7893 i, nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  c\u432 \u7901 i thu\u7853 n theo.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 c\uc0\u7909  v\u7851 n nh\u7899  chuy\u7879 n x\u432 a, mu\u7889 n k\'e9o c\u7853 u l\'ean l\u7847 u c\'f9ng m\'ecnh \u273 i Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng ni\u7879 m kinh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe th\u7845 y hai ch\u7919  "Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng" li\u7873 n c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng. C\u361 ng may th\'edm k\u7883 p th\u7901 i khuy\'ean can b\'e0: "M\u7865  \'e0, Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean v\u7845 t v\u7843  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n, m\u7865  v\u7899 i Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean ng\u7891 i tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n m\u7897 t l\'e1t, c\u417 m l\u7853 p t\u7913 c s\u7869  l\'e0m xong ngay."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 c\uc0\u7909  l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i t\u7855 t t\'e2m t\u432 , l\u7841 i k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u259 n c\u417 m b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, ch\'fa \u272 \u7895  L\'e2m \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean h\u7887 i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, h\'f4m qua con n\'f3i \u273 i nh\'e0 b\u7841 n h\u7885 c l\u7845 y t\u432  li\u7879 u, b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7911 a con c\u361 ng \u7903  b\'ean n\'e0y \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "V\'e2ng, c\u7853 u \u7845 y s\u7889 ng trong m\u7897 t c\u259 n nh\'e0 kh\'e1 l\u7899 n \u7903  khu cao nh\u7845 t ch\u7895  n\'e0y \u7841 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay \uc0\u273 ang g\u7855 p th\u7913 c \u259 n c\u7911 a \u272 \u7895  L\'e2m \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, c\'f3 ch\'fat kinh ng\u7841 c h\u7887 i: "L\'e0 c\u259 n nh\'e0 cao nh\u7845 t c\'f3 t\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7887  \u273 \u7853 m, c\u7917 a s\u7893  m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng, b\u7873  ngo\'e0i nh\'ecn phong c\'e1ch n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i? L\u7899 n g\u7847 n g\u7845 p \u273 \'f4i nh\'e0 ch\'fang ta?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u273 \u7873 u \u259 n kh\u7899 p, l\u7841 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "\u272 \'fang v\u7853 y \u7841 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7895  L\'e2m \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u361 a xu\u7889 ng, quay \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i b\'e0 tr\u7867 : "Kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang. M\u7865  \'e0, \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 nh\'e0 c\u7911 a h\u7879  th\u7889 ng l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 o c\u361  h\'e0ng x\'f3m tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7911 a cha sao? Con g\'e1i nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m xu\u7845 t ngo\u7841 i r\u7891 i m\'e0? C\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e1ng l\u7869  ph\u7843 i tr\u7889 ng ch\u7913 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7893  sung: "B\u7841 n con n\'f3i \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 nh\'e0 c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u7845 y m\'e0 l\'e0 ch\u7911  nh\'e0 cho c\u7853 u \u7845 y m\u432 \u7907 n \u7903 . C\u7853 u \u7845 y c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 c\u7853 u \u7845 y \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 nh\'e0 c\u7853 u \u7845 y c\'f3 quen v\u7899 i ch\u7911  nh\'e0."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7895  L\'e2m l\u7849 m b\u7849 m: "Nh\u432  th\u7871  l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean, ai l\u7841 i \u273 em lo\u7841 i nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3 cho con c\u7911 a b\u7841 n \u7903  ch\u7913 ... D\'f9 sao chuy\u7879 n \u7891 n \'e0o n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 c\u7911 a nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7851 n c\'f2n r\u7845 t l\u7899 n. L\'fac \u7845 y h\'ecnh nh\u432  ch\'fa v\u7915 a m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u c\'f4ng t\'e1c kh\'f4ng l\'e2u, \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  v\u7851 n c\'f2n nh\u7899  con g\'e1i nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 mang theo con r\u7875  c\'f9ng m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m th\'e2n th\'edch c\'f2n l\u7841 i qu\u7923  b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\u259 n nh\'e0 r\u7889 i r\'edt d\u7853 p \u273 \u7847 u, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng kh\'f3a c\u7917 a nh\'e0 ni\'eam phong l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'edm ph\uc0\u7909  h\u7885 a n\'f3i: "\u272 \'fang, th\'edm c\u361 ng nh\u7899  r\'f5. Khi \u273 \'f3 th\'edm v\'e0 ch\'fa con m\u7899 i quen nhau kh\'f4ng l\'e2u, l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean th\'edm \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ch\'fa, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3, v\'ec v\u7853 y \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t s\'e2u. Th\'edm c\'f2n nh\u7899  r\'f5 khi \u273 \'f3 \u259 n c\u417 m xong, ch\'fa n\'f3i mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n th\'edm \u273 i d\u7841 o xung quanh, c\u7843  hai li\u7873 n \u273 i l\'ean ph\'eda tr\'ean, \u273 i g\u7847 n n\u7917 a gi\u7901  th\'ec \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e2y quanh. L\'fac \u7845 y ch\'fa th\'edm tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i l\'f2ng \u273 \u7847 y hi\u7871 u k\u7923 , li\u7873 n chen ra ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\'ecn, nh\'ecn th\u7845 y con g\'e1i nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  d\u7851 n ng\u432 \u7901 i theo ph\'eda sau qu\u7923  tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t d\u7853 p \u273 \u7847 u v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u259 n nh\'e0, d\u7853 p li\'ean ti\u7871 p ch\'edn c\'e1i m\u7899 i d\'e1m \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y. Khi \u273 \'f3 th\'edm c\'f2n th\u7847 m ngh\u297 , nghe ch\'fa con n\'f3i con g\'e1i nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 v\u259 n h\'f3a c\'f3 h\u7885 c th\u7913 c, th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 v\u7851 n c\'f2n tin lo\u7841 i phong ki\u7871 n m\'ea t\'edn n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa n\'f3i ti\uc0\u7871 p: "Tin nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y hay kh\'f4ng v\u7899 i c\'f3 h\u7885 c v\u7845 n hay kh\'f4ng l\'e0 hai chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c nhau."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7921  nh\u7911  \u273 i\u7873 u n\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \'fang, l\'e3o s\u432  d\u7841 y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng coi tr\u7885 ng phong th\u7911 y. C\u7917 a \u273 \'f4ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\u7899 i c\u7917 a \u273 \'f4ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\u7903  \u7903  hai b\'ean m\u7897 t con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i m\u7863 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng. Nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n c\u7917 a \u273 \'f4ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 l\u7899 n vu\'f4ng v\u7913 c kh\u7855 c kh\u7849 u hi\u7879 u c\u7911 a tr\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u432 \u777 a \u273 \'f4ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh th\'ec kh\'f4ng. C\'f3 m\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian tr\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh li\'ean ti\u7871 p g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng may, h\u7847 u nh\u432  m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'ean b\'e1o, tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u th\'ec tr\u7901 i y\'ean bi\u7875 n l\u7863 ng, c\'f3 l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n n\'f3i l\'e0 t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 \u7903  c\u7893 ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ng\u259 n kh\'ed x\u7845 u l\u7841 i, v\'ec v\u7853 y \'edt phong ba.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u nghe ch\'fa th\'edm k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n n\u259 m x\u432 a c\u7911 a c\u259 n nh\'e0 kia c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t, d\'f9 sao ng\'e0y n\'e0o m\'ecnh c\u361 ng \u7903  \u273 \'f3. C\u7853 u nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u c\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\u7887 i: "Ch\'fa th\'edm, n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7871 n c\'f9ng l\'e0 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u7841 ? Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  l\'e0... l\'e0m tr\'f2?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i, ch\'fa c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  r\'f5 n\u7919 a, c\u361 ng l\'e0 sau n\'e0y nghe ng\u432 \u7901 i ta \u273 \u7891 n \u273 \u7841 i, h\'ecnh nh\u432  chuy\u7879 n nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'fac \u7845 y r\u7845 t ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p... V\'ec v\u7853 y cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7843  nh\'e0 con g\'e1i con r\u7875  tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p xu\u7845 t ngo\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 tr\uc0\u7867  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 nghi\u7879 p ch\u432 \u7899 ng c\u7911 a con trai nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 tu\u7893 i chung quy lu\'f4n th\'edch h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng chuy\u7879 n c\u361 , h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngay l\u7853 p t\u7913 c, c\'e0ng l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n ng\'e0y x\u432 a, khi b\u7843 n th\'e2n tu\u7893 i c\'f2n tr\u7867  th\'ec c\'e0ng ph\u7843 i nh\u7899 , kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  nh\u7899  m\'e0 c\'f2n th\'edch k\u7875  cho ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c. B\'e0 tr\u7867  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\u7879 , chuy\u7879 n h\u417 n hai m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c n\'e0y b\'e0 v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  k\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\'e0nh m\u7841 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7889 n l\'e0 \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  c\u7911 a \'f4ng c\u7909  nh\'e0 n\u7885  c\'f4ng t\'e1c v\u7899 i \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  c\u7911 a ch\u7891 ng b\'e0 tr\u7867  c\'f3 ch\'fat li\'ean quan, v\'ec v\u7853 y chuy\u7879 n nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta l\'fac \u7845 y b\'e0 tr\u7867  th\'f4ng qua ch\u7891 ng m\'ecnh c\u361 ng nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \'edt n\u7897 i t\'ecnh. V\u7907  \'f4ng c\u7909  b\u7883  b\u7879 nh \u273 \'e3 qua \u273 \u7901 i, d\u432 \u7899 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t trai m\u7897 t g\'e1i, tu\u7893 i t\'e1c so v\u7899 i ch\'fa kh\'f4ng ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch l\u7855 m, h\u417 i l\u7899 n h\u417 n ch\'fa m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 l\u7853 p gia \u273 \'ecnh. Con g\'e1i v\'e0 ch\u7891 ng \u7903  n\u417 i kh\'e1c, con trai con d\'e2u v\'e0 \'f4ng c\u7909  th\'ec s\u7889 ng chung trong c\u259 n nh\'e0 ph\'eda tr\'ean kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  sau m\u7897 t n\u259 m n\u7885  v\u7907  c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i con trai ho\'e0i thai, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n, gi\u7845 u v\u7907  t\'ecm t\'ecnh nh\'e2n b\'ean ngo\'e0i. T\'ecnh nh\'e2n \u273 \'f3 v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i con trai l\'e0m c\'f9ng \u273 \u417 n v\u7883 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ha\u803 ng ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i l\u432 \u417 ng thi\'ea\u803 n, c\'f2n l\u7845 y th\'e2n ph\u7853 n \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p c\'f9ng m\u7845 y \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p kh\'e1c t\u7899 i nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885 . Trong l\'f2ng c\'f4 ta c\u361 ng ghen gh\'e9t ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7907 , th\u7915 a c\u417  \u273 em m\u7897 t t\u7901  gi\u7845 y \u273 \u7887  v\u7869  t\u7909  t\'e0 tr\u7853 n b\u7887  d\u432 \u7899 i chi\u7871 c \u273 \u7879 m ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7907  th\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba b\uc0\u7889 n th\'e1ng sau, ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7907  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'f3 d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u chuy\u7875 n d\u7841 , b\u7903 i v\'ec l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\u432 a d\u7921  li\u7879 u tr\u432 \u7899 c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  v\u7897 i v\'e0ng m\u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n nh\'e0 xem. L\'fac \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u7867  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\'f3 v\u7853 t g\'ec \u273 \'f3 t\u7915  trong b\u7909 ng \u273 i ra, b\u7909 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7907  c\u361 ng nh\u7887  xu\u7889 ng\'97\'97 nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y "Thai nhi" \u273 \'f3 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n n\'e0y qu\u7843  th\u7921 c qu\'e1 qu\u7927  d\u7883 , ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7907  sau khi bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kinh s\u7907 , nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c trong nh\'e0 c\u361 ng s\u7907  h\'e3i kh\'f4n t\u7843 , li\'ean t\u7909 c d\u7863 n d\'f2 m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u7867  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7875  l\u7897 . V\u7873  sau \'f4ng c\u7909  gi\'fap con g\'e1i m\u7901 i m\u7897 t v\u7883  cao nh\'e2n t\u7899 i, v\u7883  cao nh\'e2n n\u7885  nghe n\'f3i l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i hi\u7871 m hoi \u273 \'e3 v\u432 \u7907 t qua nh\u7919 ng b\u7845 t \u7893 n ch\'ednh tr\u7883  t\u7915  r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c, tu\u7893 i \u273 \'e3 t\u7847 m b\u7843 y m\u432 \u417 i, qu\u7843  th\u7853 t c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7843 n l\u297 nh, sau khi \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  li\u7873 n t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7901  gi\u7845 y t\u7909  t\'e0 tr\u7853 n \u273 \u7863 t d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7879 m kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7921 a theo \u273 \u7847 u m\u7889 i \u273 \'f3 r\u7891 i l\u7841 i s\'e0ng l\u7885 c, c\u7897 ng th\'eam ng\u432 \u7901 i con trai kia sau khi tr\u7843 i qua tai h\u7885 a l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 s\u7907  h\'e3i b\u7921 c n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i \'e1p l\u7921 c, chuy\u7879 n h\u7855 n ngo\u7841 i t\'ecnh li\u7873 n b\u7841 i l\u7897 . T\'ecnh nh\'e2n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\u361 ng th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n t\u7909  t\'e0 tr\u7853 n kia l\'e0 m\'ecnh t\'ecnh c\u7901  mua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  m\u7897 t thu\u7853 t s\u297  m\u7855 t m\'f9 b\'e0y qu\'e1n b\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u361 ng t\'ecm kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y thu\u7853 t s\u297  \u273 \'f3; nh\u432 ng thanh minh n\'f3i b\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u7881  l\'e0 ghen gh\'e9t qu\u7845 y ph\'e1, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7901  gi\u7845 y kia r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f3 h\u7919 u d\u7909 ng hay kh\'f4ng n\'ean m\u7899 i b\u7887  d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7879 m, kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  l\u7841 i g\'e2y ra h\u7853 u qu\u7843  nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Vi\uc0\u7879 c n\'e0y chung quy l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i nghe kinh s\u7907 , l\u7841 i c\'f3 d\u7845 u v\u7871 t c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c cho n\'ean v\u7851 n c\'f3 tin \u273 \u7891 n truy\u7873 n ra. \'d4ng c\u7909  lu\'f4n xem tr\u7885 ng th\u7875  di\u7879 n, sau khi nghe chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a con trai li\u7873 n t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh nh\u7853 p vi\u7879 n; ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7907  c\u361 ng t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i s\u7907  h\'e3i kh\'f4ng th\'f4i, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ly h\'f4n d\u7885 n v\u7873  nh\'e0 m\u7865  \u273 \u7867 ; c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i l\'e0 b\'e1o \u7913 ng h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i hay kh\'f4ng, ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n v\'e0i ng\'e0y sau khi ly h\'f4n, ng\u432 \u7901 i con trai kia v\u7899 i t\'ecnh nh\'e2n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'fac \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i g\u7863 p tai n\u7841 n giao th\'f4ng, t\u7917  vong t\u7841 i ch\u7895 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean c\u7917 a n\'e1t nh\'e0 tan, ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i m\u7897 t c\'f4 con g\'e1i m\u7897 t m\u7863 t \u7903  b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n ch\u259 m s\'f3c cha gi\'e0, m\u7897 t m\u7863 t th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng quay v\u7873  nh\'e0 gi\'fap d\u7885 n d\u7865 p qu\u7843 n l\'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 con g\'e1i b\uc0\u7853 n r\u7897 n c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c, ph\u7843 i ch\u259 m s\'f3c gia \u273 \'ecnh nh\u7887  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, c\'f2n ph\u7843 i th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean \u273 i b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n ch\u259 m s\'f3c cha, m\u432 \u7901 i ng\'e0y n\u7917 a th\'e1ng m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  quay v\u7873  c\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3 x\u7917  l\'fd m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, ti\u7879 n th\u7875  l\u7845 y m\u7897 t \'edt \u273 \u7891  cha th\u432 \u7901 ng d\'f9ng. K\u7923  qu\'e1i ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7895 i l\u7847 n c\'f4 tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 \u7873 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u259 n nh\'e0 gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903 , l\u7847 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n hai kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y, th\u7901 i gian l\'e2u d\'e0i li\u7873 n ph\'e1t gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 con g\'e1i l\uc0\u7841 i m\u7901 i v\u7883  cao nh\'e2n kia t\u7899 i gi\'fap nh\'ecn nh\'e0 m\'ecnh. Cao nh\'e2n kia sau khi v\'e0o c\u7917 a nh\'ecn xung quanh m\u7897 t ch\'fat, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m g\'e2y r\u7855 c r\u7889 i, l\u7863 ng l\u7869  k\'e9o c\'f4 con g\'e1i ra ngo\'e0i r\u7891 i m\u7899 i n\'f3i cho c\'f4 bi\u7871 t ng\u7885 n ngu\u7891 n. Nghe n\'f3i b\u7903 i v\'ec \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7911 a t\u7909  t\'e0 tr\u7853 n kia, thai nhi b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng s\u7889 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, sinh ra ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\u7917  thai, nh\u432 ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7913  gi\u7889 ng t\'e0 linh m\u432 \u7907 n l\'fac ch\u7883  d\'e2u c\'f4 sinh con g\u7917 i h\u7891 n v\'e0o, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  h\u7859 n l\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  \u273 \u7875  \u273 i, li\u7873 n \u7903  l\u7841 i c\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u m\u7845 y l\u7847 n c\'f4 tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh an v\'f4 s\u7921  v\u7899 i th\u7913  kia, ch\u7913 ng t\u7887  n\'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e2m h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, hu\u7889 ng chi v\u7889 n l\'e0 do ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'e2y chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u432 a n\'f3 t\u7899 i, c\u7913 ng r\u7855 n \u273 \u432 a \u273 i ch\u7881  s\u7907  kh\'f4ng d\u7877 . Ch\'ednh cao nh\'e2n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \'f4\u803 ng t\u7899 i n\'f3, ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7901 i \u7845 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  ra ai c\'f3 th\u7875  x\u7917  l\'fd \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Th\'f4i c\u7913  l\'e0m nghi l\u7877  cung k\'ednh \u273 em nh\'e0 cho n\'f3 m\u432 \u7907 n \u7903 , sau \u273 \'f3 ni\'eam phong nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng cho ai v\'e0o l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, n\'f3 \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y l\'e0m xong b\u7843 n th\'e2n chuy\u7879 n mu\u7889 n l\'e0m s\u7869  t\u7921  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 con g\'e1i nghe l\uc0\u7901 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ni\'eam phong nh\'e0, m\'e0 \'f4ng c\u7909  v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 tu\u7893 i, l\u7841 i tr\u7843 i qua chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y m\u7897 t th\'e2n b\u7879 nh kh\'f4ng d\u7853 y n\u7893 i, r\u7845 t nhanh li\u7873 n \u273 i. Con g\'e1i x\u7917  l\'fd h\u7853 u s\u7921  c\u7911 a cha xong, kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u c\u361 ng c\'f9ng ch\u7891 ng ra n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i, nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng ch\u432 a nghe n\'f3i tr\u7903  v\u7873 , v\u7853 y n\'ean theo l\u7869  th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3 h\u7859 n l\'e0 v\u7851 n \u273 ang b\u7883  ni\'eam phong l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe xong trong ng\uc0\u7921 c c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7845 t an, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  trong c\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3 l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, cho t\u7899 i gi\u7901  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng ph\'e1t gi\'e1c d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u c\'f3 "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" th\u7913  ba t\u7891 n t\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\u7901 i cao nh\'e2n m\'e0 b\'e0 tr\u7867  k\u7875  hay kh\'f4ng, th\u7913  kia \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m xong chuy\u7879 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n mu\u7889 n l\'e0m n\'ean \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i b\u7897  d\u7841 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'ecnh th\u7843 n ki\'ean \u273 \u7883 nh an \u7911 i m\'ecnh "Th\u7871  gian n\'e0y c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 qu\u7927 ", th\u7847 m ngh\u297  d\'f9 khi \u273 \'f3 ch\u7911  nh\'e0 c\'f3 n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tin, \u7903  nh\u7901  c\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec l\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fa th\'edm nghe xong c\uc0\u361 ng khuy\'ean nh\u7911 : "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean \'e0, con n\'f3i vi\u7879 c n\'e0y v\u7899 i b\u7841 n con m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ch\'fang ta c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i phong ki\u7871 n m\'ea t\'edn, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n coi tr\u7885 ng chuy\u7879 n t\'e2m an m\'e0, d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 nh\'e0 \u273 \'e3 cho qu\u7927  th\u7847 n m\u432 \u7907 n, n\'ean chuy\u7875 n ra th\'ec t\u7889 t h\u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u \u7845 y kh\'f4ng tin nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 \'e2u." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, gi\u7843  b\u7897  nh\u432  t\'f2 m\'f2 h\u7887 i, "Ch\'fa th\'edm, nh\'e0 m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n linh d\u7883  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Ch\'fa xua xua tay: "Kh\uc0\u7909 , nh\'e0 ch\'fang ta l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i hay l\'e0m vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7873 u ch\'ednh tr\u7921 c, kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec sai tr\'e1i, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7909 ng ch\u7841 m \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng t\'e1n d\u432 \u417 ng ch\'fa th\'edm hai c\'e2u, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  qu\u7843  nhi\'ean \u273 \'eam h\'e8 n\u259 m \u7845 y th\u7913  b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y ch\u7881  l\'e0 ch\u7885 c gh\u7865 o m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
