\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \uc0\u7903  nh\'e0 ch\'fa qu\'e1 l\'e2u, l\u7845 y c\u7899  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c c\'f2n c\'f3 vi\u7879 c xong r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, sau khi \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng quay l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 nhanh ch\'f3ng chu\u7891 n v\u7873  nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\u7845 y ch\'eca kho\'e1 m\u7903  c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch kh\'f4ng th\uc0\u7845 y ai, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i t\u7915  trong ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p truy\u7873 n ra m\'f9i s\u7919 a th\u417 m ng\'e0o ng\u7841 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean thay gi\'e0y c\uc0\u7903 i \'e1o kho\'e1c \u273 i v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p, qu\u7843  nhi\'ean tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o len tr\u7855 ng d\'e0i tay \u273 ang t\u7921 a l\u432 ng v\'e0o t\u7911  b\'e1t xem \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, \'e1nh m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i m\'e0u v\'e0ng chi\u7871 u xu\u7889 ng b\'e0n \u259 n m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh h\u7855 n, l\'f2 n\u432 \u7899 ng ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 ang ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng "\'d9 \'f9", t\u7887 a ra m\'f9i s\u7919 a ng\u7885 t \u273 \u7853 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u m\u7899 i bu\'f4ng di \u273 \u7897 ng xu\u7889 ng, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "L\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3i mu\u7889 n l\'e0m b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t, h\'f4m nay v\u7915 a v\u7863 n c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian r\u7843 nh n\'ean l\'e0m th\u7917 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n phi\u7873 n h\'e0 v\u7853 y \u273 \'e2u... \u272 i ti\u7879 m b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t mua ho\u7863 c g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n \u273 \u7863 t b\'e1nh l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0." Trong t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\'e0m b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t r\u7847 y r\'e0 h\u417 n l\'e0m c\u417 m n\u7845 u th\u7913 c \u259 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng phi\uc0\u7873 n, l\'e0m \u7903  nh\'e0 an to\'e0n s\u7841 ch s\u7869  h\u417 n mua ngo\'e0i, s\u7919 a t\'f4i d\'f9ng c\u361 ng t\u7889 t h\u417 n." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i li\u7871 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean, "Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean l\'ean l\u7847 u thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 i, b\'e1nh s\u7855 p ch\'edn r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean thay qu\uc0\u7847 n \'e1o xong qu\u7843  nhi\'ean b\'e1nh \u273 \'e3 ch\'edn, l\'e0 b\'e1nh ph\'f4 mai th\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\u432 ng m\'f9i v\u7883  thanh h\u417 n so v\u7899 i mua ngo\'e0i, kh\'f4ng ng\u7885 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u361 ng tinh t\u234 \u769  ti\u777  mi\u777  h\u417 n. B\'e1nh v\u7889 n n\'ean b\u7887  v\'e0o t\u7911  l\u7841 nh l\'e0m m\'e1t m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7855 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng \u273 \u7863 t v\'e0o khay cho c\u7853 u n\u7871 m th\u7917 , xong m\u7899 i b\u7887  ph\u7847 n c\'f2n l\u7841 i v\'e0o trong t\u7911  l\u7841 nh l\'e0m m\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng b\u7855 t ch\u432 \u7899 c c\u7855 t m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng nh\u7887  \u273 \'fat v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i nh\u7899  t\u7899 i ch\'ednh s\u7921 , k\u7875  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  ch\u7895  b\'e0 tr\u7867  v\u7873  c\u259 n nh\'e0 n\'e0y cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\u7843  nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng h\u7873  l\u432 u t\'e2m: "\u272 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 bao nhi\'eau n\u259 m r\u7891 i, h\u417 n n\u7919 a lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7891 n \u273 \u7841 i n\'e0y b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng l\'e0 th\'eam m\u7855 m th\'eam mu\u7889 i nghe nh\u7847 m \u273 \u7891 n b\u7853 y." R\'f5 r\'e0ng cho th\u7845 y th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  coi nh\u432  chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f9a kh\'f4ng th\'e8m \u273 \u7875  \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f3e m\uc0\u7855 t h\u7855 n h\u417 i cong l\'ean nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "C\u7853 u th\u7871  m\'e0 c\u361 ng tin."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7875 u ng\u7889 c t\u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ch\uc0\u7919  sau l\u7841 i b\u7883  h\u7855 n th\'e2n m\u7853 t ng\u7853 m v\'e0o trong \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n c\'f2n mu\u7889 n tranh lu\u7853 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i x\u7855 n m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng \u273 \'fat v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng c\u7853 u: "H\u417 n n\u7919 a, t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec, c\u7853 u m\u7899 i \u7903  m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n trong nh\'e0 n\'e0y c\'f2n c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7899 m \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u7871 t qu\u7843  s\u7869  l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y, h\u417 n n\u7919 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  ch\u7895  b\'e0 tr\u7867 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3 lu\u7853 n c\u7913  g\'ec h\'f9ng h\u7891 n, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng tranh lu\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u361 ng li\u7873 n th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7875  tr\'ean b\'e0n b\'ean c\u7841 nh \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean vang l\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i qua c\u7847 m l\u7845 y, m\'e0n h\'ecnh b\'e1o ch\'ednh l\'e0 C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\'e2u c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m vui s\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng c\u7911 a con g\'e1i vang l\'ean t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u kia \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i: "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, h\'f4m nay l\'e0 l\u7877  \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i em h\u7865 n m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng \u273 i \u259 n, anh c\u361 ng \u273 i nh\'e9?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng, kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7913  \u273 i ch\u417 i \u273 i." B\u7841 n b\'e8 c\u7911 a C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng quen bi\u7871 t l\u7855 m, \u273 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec vui, hu\u7889 ng chi b\'e2y gi\u7901  th\u7901 i bu\u7893 i r\u7889 i ren, c\u7853 u n\'e0o d\'e1m \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i qu\'e1 mu\u7897 n ho\u7863 c l\'e0 \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng v\u7873  ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7891 i cho n\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 i ch\u417 i ng\'e0y l\u7877  \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n sao?" Gi\u7885 ng n\u7919  b\'ean kia l\'e0m nh\u432  c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f9a h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c li\u7871 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i, ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u7903  chung v\u7899 i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng... N\'f3i chung m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i ch\u417 i \u273 i, anh kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c2m l\uc0\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\u7887 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe \u273 \u7889 i tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i r\'f5 r\'e0ng, th\u7845 y c\u7853 u c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\u7899 i h\u417 i nh\'edu m\'e0y n\'f3i: "L\u7841 i l\'e0 C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch kia? C\u7853 u c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i c\'f4 ta \'edt th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u v\'ec sao Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng \u432 a C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\u7855 n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i tuy r\u7857 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\'e2n thi\u7879 n, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch l\u7841 i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t l\u7841 nh nh\u7841 t. Nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao b\'e2y gi\u7901  Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n thu\u7853 n theo \'fd c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, b\'e8n n\'f3i: "Em \u7845 y k\'eau t\'f4i bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 i \u259 n, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 ." L\'fac n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i d\u7883 u th\u7847 n s\u7855 c xu\u7889 ng, "Bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i \u259 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i m\u7885 i th\u7913  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n y\'ean \u7893 n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ba ng\'e0y sau th\u7847 y h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i d\uc0\u7889 i qu\u7843  nhi\'ean s\u7869  g\u7863 p b\'e1o \u7913 ng, th\u7847 y h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  l\'fac n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  giao cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  kh\u7849 n c\u7845 p, do c\u7853 u v\'e0 hai s\u432  huynh c\'f9ng ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch, nh\'ecn qua nhanh nh\u7845 t c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i ba ng\'e0y m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  ho\'e0n th\'e0nh, l\u7847 n n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u7903  c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh n\u432 \u417 ng nh\u7901  nh\'e0 h\u7855 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin n\'e0y trong l\'f2ng c\u361 ng c\'f3 ch\'fat s\u7907  h\'e3i, theo l\u7901 i H\u7891  Tinh n\'f3i \'edt nh\u7845 t s\u7869  c\'f2n ba ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, nh\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  H\u7891  Tinh v\'e0 c\u7843 nh s\'e1t b\'ean kia \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng t\'ecm ra manh m\u7889 i hung th\u7911 , \u273 i\u7875 m chung duy nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \u7873 u sinh s\u7889 ng quanh khu v\u7921 c g\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p x\'fac\'97\'97 nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u n\'f3 l\'e0 y\'eau t\'e0 h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean n\'f3 s\u7869  b\u7887  m\u7863 c l\u7877  ph\'e1p m\u7863 c s\u7913 c l\'e0m theo \'fd m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u259 n c\u7913  theo kinh nghi\u7879 m l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh o\'e1n qu\u7927  h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\u361 ng c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng m\u7841 nh, m\u7909 c ti\'eau c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u s\u7907  c\'f2n ch\u432 a t\'ecm ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c y\'eau t\'e0 kia, b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng o\'e1n qu\u7927  n\'e0y h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7849 n th\u7853 n d\'e8 ch\u7915 ng h\u7887 i d\'f2 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, th\u7847 y h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n c\u7911 a t\'f4i giao vi\u7879 c cho t\'f4i, m\u7845 y ng\'e0y t\u7899 i t\'f4i ph\u7843 i quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng... C\u7853 u c\'f3 mu\u7889 n quay v\u7873  \u7903  chung v\u7899 i t\'f4i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i h\u7887 i l\u7841 i c\u7853 u: "C\u7853 u mu\u7889 n t\'f4i quay v\u7873 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i cho h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t c\'e1i n\'e0y l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n y\'eau t\'e0 qu\u7927  qu\'e1i, v\'ec v\u7853 y ch\u7881  thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "\u7914 ... \u7902  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh h\u417 i c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n, v\u7851 n l\'e0 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  c\'f9ng th\'ec t\u7889 t h\u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7889 n \u273 ang m\u7897 t tay n\'e2ng m\'e1 ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t m\'ecnh, nghe v\u7853 y li\u7873 n bu\'f4ng tay xu\u7889 ng, th\u7859 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7853 y n\'f3i: "V\u7853 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, t\'f4i v\'e0 c\u7853 u c\'f9ng tr\u7903  v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'ed do g\'ec \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c chen chung tr\'ean m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u417 n, v\u7851 n l\'e0 ai ng\u7911  gi\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  chung trong m\u7897 t c\u259 n ph\'f2ng, n\'e2ng m\u7855 t l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y qu\'e1 s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ai ng\uc0\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i th\u7913  ba t\u7915  khi chuy\u7875 n v\u7873 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang ng\u7911  say, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  n\u7857 m gh\'e9 v\'e0o l\u7895  tai c\u7853 u k\'eau t\'ean c\u7853 u: "... Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng "H\u7903 " l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t c\'e2u n\'f3i \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe \u7903  \u273 \'e2u \u273 \'f3, n\'f3i l\'e0 n\u7871 u nghe th\u7845 y thanh \'e2m g\u7885 i t\'ean m\'ecnh m\'e0 kh\'f4ng r\'f5 n\u417 i ph\'e1t ra th\'ec nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f9y ti\u7879 n \u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7843  kinh, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c m\u7903  to m\u7855 t, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" \u273 ang ng\u7891 i \u7903  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, t\'f3c d\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en r\u7911  xu\u7889 ng t\u7915  hai b\'ean m\u7863 t, m\u432 \u7901 i ng\'f3n tay d\'e0i nh\u7887  m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean hai vai c\u7853 u, mang theo h\u417 i l\u7841 nh v\'e0 t\u7917  kh\'ed th\u7845 u x\u432 \u417 ng, c\'f2n tho\'e1ng c\'f3 m\'f9i tanh h\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f4 ta" \uc0\u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t ch\'ednh di\u7879 n v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u7871 ch m\'f4i, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch qu\u7927  d\u7883 , n\u417 i h\u7889 c m\u7855 t r\u7891 i l\u7841 i t\u7889 i om, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7847 u l\'e2u\'97\'97 "C\'f4 ta" kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u7903  trong s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7921 c \u273 \u7897  l\u7841 i nh\'ecn ra v\'e0i ph\u7847 n quen thu\u7897 c t\u7915  g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t n\'e0y, tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng g\u7863 p m\u7863 t, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, \'edt nh\u7845 t khi c\'f2n s\u7889 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'fang l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u quen.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7853 t gi\u7853 t mi\u7879 ng, trong mi\u7879 ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u432  b\u7883  b\u7883 t b\'f4ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e2m thanh n\'e0o. C\u7853 u n\u7895  l\u7921 c d\'f9ng s\u7913 c t\u7915  trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng ngh\u7865 n ra hai ti\u7871 ng: "... Gi\u7843 n Doanh?"\cb1 \
