\cf2 \cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia l\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng v\'ec c\'e1i t\'ean n\'e0y m\'e0 thay \u273 \u7893 i, hai m\'f3ng tay x\'e1m tr\u7855 ng b\'e1m tr\'ean vai Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng b\u7845 m c\'e0ng s\'e2u, \'e1nh m\u7855 t tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3 \uc0\u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t o\'e1n qu\u7927  kh\'f4ng ch\'fat l\'fd t\'ednh, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i t\'ecnh, so v\u7899 i c\'f4 g\'e1i tr\u7847 m l\u7863 ng th\u7865 n th\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7863 p l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0 hai th\u7913  b\u7845 t \u273 \u7891 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y hai con m\u7855 t kia c\'e1ch m\'ecnh c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, \'e2m thanh ch\'f3i tai nh\u432  s\'f3ng \u273 i\u7879 n radio c\u361  k\u7929  \u273 \u7913 t qu\'e3ng, mang theo m\u7897 t ch\'fat t\u7841 p \'e2m "Ee...eee...eeee" gh\'e9 v\'e0o l\u7895  tai c\u7853 u vang l\'ean \'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7871 t... V\'ec sao... Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 m\'e0y..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e1ng ch\u7871 t nh\u7845 t... L\'e0 m\'e0y..."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t c\u417 n \u7899 n l\u7841 nh d\'e2ng l\'ean t\u7915  trong ng\u7921 c, c\u7853 u r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c bi\u7871 t \'e2m thanh t\'ea t\'ea...\'ea...eeee o\'e1n \u273 \u7897 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  s\'f3ng nhi\u7877 u tr\u432 \u7899 c kia nghe th\u7845 y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 ang n\'f3i g\'ec \'97\'97 ch\'fang \u273 ang h\u7887 i c\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t v\'ec sao kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 m\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\'e3y gi\uc0\u7909 a quay \u273 \u7847 u, h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda gi\u432 \u7901 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, g\u7855 ng s\u7913 c nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda h\u7855 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m c\u7885 ng c\u7887  c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u nh\'ecn t\'f4i \u273 i, li\u7871 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 i... D\'f9 ch\u7881  l\'e0 li\u7871 c nh\'ecn, c\u7847 u xin c\u7853 u...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7893  h\u7885 ng c\u7853 u c\u7845 p t\u7889 c co r\'fat, hao h\u7871 t kh\'ed l\u7921 c l\u7841 i ch\u7881  gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a phun ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ch\u7919  "Di\u7879 p".\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u vai b\u7883  si\u7871 t, kh\'ed l\u7921 c to\'e0n th\'e2n d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  r\'fat \u273 i khi th\u7913  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o tanh t\u432 \u7903 i kia l\u7841 i g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\'e2n th\u7875  m\'ecnh h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\u361 ng c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng l\u7841 nh, g\u7847 n nh\u432  s\u7855 p h\'f2a l\'e0m m\u7897 t th\u7875  v\u7899 i th\u7913  kia.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi..."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec sao c\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn t\'f4i?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\u7895  l\u7921 c mu\u7889 n duy tr\'ec thanh t\u7881 nh, nh\u432 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\'f4 l\u7921 c t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7907 t t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7907 t gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  thanh s\u7855 t l\u7899 n \'e9p c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'e1ch" m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7915 ng s\'e1ng, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i theo \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng ch\u7907 t nh\u7865  \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  m\u7855 t, th\u7845 y \u273 \'e8n ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7903 , c\u7843  ph\'f2ng s\'e1ng r\'f5, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng c\u7847 m tay c\u7853 u, k\'eau t\'ean c\u7853 u: "Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean? L\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? Th\u7845 y \'e1c m\u7897 ng \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7901  m\u7883 t m\u7903  hai m\u7855 t th\u7853 t l\u7899 n nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang x\'e1c nh\u7853 n ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i. C\u7853 u nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, o\'e1n qu\u7927  dung m\u7841 o gi\u7889 ng Gi\u7843 n Doanh kia \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng tuy\u7879 t v\u7885 ng qu\'e1 m\u7913 c, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t m\'ecnh l\'fac n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ch\u7853 m r\'e3i r\'fat tay c\'f2n l\u7841 i t\u7915  trong ch\u259 n ra tr\'f9m l\'ean b\'e0n tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang n\u7855 m tay m\'ecnh, g\u7855 t gao si\u7871 t, th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi da th\u7883 t c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\u7899 p x\u432 \u417 ng quen thu\u7897 c m\u7899 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n b\'ecnh t\u297 nh l\u7841 i, t\u7921 a h\u7891  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a v\u7873  t\u7899 i nh\'e2n gian.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\'f4 th\u7913 c c\u7847 m b\'e0n tay \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean m\'e1 m\'ecnh vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  m\u7897 t l\'e1t. \u272 \u7897 ng t\'e1c tuy r\u7857 ng \u7845 u tr\u297  nh\u432 ng khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y an to\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u417 i co m\u7897 t c\'e1i, l\u7841 i r\u7845 t nhanh bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng ra, m\u7863 c c\u7853 u c\u7847 m trong tay \'e1p l\'ean m\u7863 t ng\u417  ng\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 n n\u7917 a ng\'e0y m\u7899 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n h\u7891 i th\u7847 n l\u7841 i, v\u7851 n c\'f3 ch\'fat ng\'e2y ng\u7889 c tr\u7915 ng m\u7855 t nh\'ecn, l\u7841 i nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng g\u7885 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7913 t kho\'e1t b\'f2 l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7857 m nghi\'eang b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u: "L\'e0 t\'f4i. A Di\'ean, l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n du\u7895 i tay ch\u7845 m nh\u7865  l\'ean kh\'f3e m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "C\u7853 u c\'e1i d\u7841 ng n\'e0y... gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  r\u7845 t \u7911 y khu\u7845 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7910 y khu\u7845 t? Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 b\u7897  d\'e1ng g\'ec, nh\u432 ng r\u7845 t t\u7921  nhi\'ean \'e1p l\u7841 i g\u7847 n, k\u7873  s\'e1t kh\'ed t\u7913 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n quen thu\u7897 c, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i y\'ean l\u7863 ng n\u7857 m \u7903  \u273 \'f3, t\u7915 ng ch\'fat t\u7915 ng ch\'fat \u273 em c\u7843 m x\'fac v\'e0 t\'e2m t\'ecnh v\u7915 a r\u7891 i bu\'f4ng tr\'f4i \u273 i h\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e3i l\'fac l\'e2u sau c\uc0\u7853 u m\u7899 i nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n tr\u7885 ng y\u7871 u: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  Gi\u7843 n Doanh kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 l\u7869  con b\'e9... b\u7883  gi\u7871 t r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng n\u7871 u Gi\u7843 n Doanh th\u7853 t s\u7921  b\u7883  gi\u7871 t, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u361 ng h\u417 n ph\'e2n n\u7917 a l\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\u7913 u v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 ch\'fat nghi ho\u7863 c nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n b\u7883 a: "V\u7915 a r\u7891 i t\'f4i g\u7863 p \'e1c m\u7897 ng, th\u7845 y con b\'e9 b\u7883  gi\u7871 t... C\'f2n b\u7883  m\'f3c m\u7855 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 a di \u273 \u7897 ng qua: "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng g\'ec v\u7899 i c\'e1i t\'ean n\'e0y, n\u7871 u c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  lo l\u7855 ng th\'ec th\u7917  g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i h\u7887 i b\u7841 n c\'f4 b\'e9 xem."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 b\u7841 n c\'f9ng l\u7899 p c\u7911 a C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean \u273 i c\'f9ng nhau, c\'f2n c\'f9ng C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch t\u7899 i ph\'f2ng ch\'fang ta, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\u7845 t tr\u7847 m t\'ednh." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7855 c cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7899 . K\u7923  th\u7853 t ch\'ednh c\u7853 u v\u7899 i Gi\u7843 n Doanh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng quen bi\u7871 t m\u7845 y, l\'e0 th\'f4ng qua C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch m\'e0 bi\u7871 t nhau, n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n c\u361 ng ch\u432 a h\u417 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u259 m c\'e2u, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i khi g\u7863 p l\u7841 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i l\'e0 c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng nh\u432  th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891 , 3:34, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 th\u7901 i gian t\u7889 t \u273 \u7875  g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng *nh\'e2n m\u7879 nh quan thi\'ean, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u. C\u7853 u c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\u7903  danh b\u7841 , nh\u432 ng l\'fac t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ba ch\u7919  "C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch" l\u7841 i ch\u7847 n ch\u7901  \'97\'97 m\'ecnh l\'e0 m\u7909 c ti\'eau c\u7911 a y\'eau v\u7853 t kia, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  Gi\u7843 n Doanh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i, m\'e0 \u273 i\u7875 m giao duy nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 con b\'e9, ch\'ednh l\'e0 C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (nh\'e2n m\uc0\u7879 nh quan thi\'ean: th\'e0nh ng\u7919  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n m\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec kh\'f4ng th\u7875  coi th\u432 \u7901 ng)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y... li\u7879 u c\'f3 ph\u7843 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng m\u7909 c ti\'eau kh\'f4ng, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  con b\'e9 c\'f3 an to\'e0n kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng n\u7871 u... con b\'e9 ch\'ednh l\'e0 hung th\u7911  th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd ngh\uc0\u297  n\'e0y \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n trong \u273 \u7847 u khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng r\'e9t m\'e0 run, nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u432  c\u7887  d\u7841 i \u273 i\'ean cu\u7891 ng sinh tr\u432 \u7903 ng \'97\'97 n\u7871 u ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u \u273 ang mu\u7889 n li\'ean l\u7841 c l\'fac n\'e0y c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1ng s\u7907  h\u417 n l\'e0 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\u7855 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 ng c\u7913  m\u7841 nh m\u7869  n\'e0o c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\u7843 n b\'e1c \'fd ni\u7879 m n\'e0y trong \u273 \u7847 u. C\u7853 u v\'e0 C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch v\u7889 n quen tr\'ean m\u7841 ng, ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7901 i giao t\'ecnh kh\'f4ng s\'e2u, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i xu\u7845 t th\'e2n, lai l\u7883 ch, ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 c\u7911 a c\'f4... c\u7853 u ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t g\'ec h\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng ng\u7891 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh b\u7891 i c\u7853 u, c\u7847 m di \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\u7853 t xem, sau khi th\u7845 y m\u7897 t tin t\u7913 c ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean... Tin v\u7915 a m\u7899 i nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t thi th\u7875  thi\u7871 u n\u7919  kh\'f4ng m\u7855 t trong con h\u7867 m nh\u7887  ngo\'e0i c\u7893 ng \u273 \'f4ng, ghi nh\u7853 n ban \u273 \u7847 u l\'e0 m\u7897 t sinh vi\'ean khoa Ngo\u7841 i ng\u7919  tr\u432 \u7901 ng ch\'fang ta, \u273 \u7883 a \u273 i\u7875 m v\u7913 t x\'e1c kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7883 a \u273 i\u7875 m g\'e2y \'e1n, nh\u7919 ng v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  kh\'e1c v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 ang \u273 i\u7873 u tra."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng l\u7901 i c\'f2n l\u7841 i h\u7855 n ch\u432 a n\'f3i h\u7871 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u r\'f5 \'fd h\u7855 n, ng\'f3n tay ph\'eda tr\'ean c\'e1i t\'ean "C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch" r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c nh\u7845 n xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i k\u7871 t n\u7889 i "T\'edt \'97\'97 t\'edt \'97\'97" vang l\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "\u272 \u7875  t\'f4i h\u7887 i th\u7917 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u \uc0\u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 p, gi\u7885 ng C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\'f3 ch\'fat kinh ng\u7841 c: "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean? Sao mu\u7897 n th\u7871  n\'e0y r\u7891 i l\u7841 i g\u7885 i cho em? C\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\uc0\u7879 c g\'ec," Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7889  g\u7855 ng duy tr\'ec ng\u7919  kh\'ed b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, "Anh ch\u432 a ng\u7911 , v\u7915 a m\u7899 i th\u7845 y tin n\'f3i khoa ngo\u7841 i ng\u7919  c\'f3 m\u7897 t n\u7919  sinh x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n, mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i th\u259 m em c\'f3 sao kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\'c0... Em kh\'f4ng sao, c\'e1m \uc0\u417 n anh." Trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7885 ng c\u7911 a C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, ch\u7881  nghe c\'f4 h\u417 i nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i, "Nh\u432 ng m\'e0, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 Gi\u7843 n Doanh g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 G\uc0\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 Gi\u7843 n Doanh. Qu\u7843  nhi\'ean l\'e0 Gi\u7843 n Doanh.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i v\u7851 n b\'ecnh an v\'f4 s\u7921 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m m\u7855 t, an \u7911 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch h\u7891 i l\'e2u r\u7891 i c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i. C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4ng tin m\'ecnh mu\u7889 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean nh\u7871 ch kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Th\u7853 t bi\u7871 t d\u7895  d\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, tr\'e1ch kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u432 \u7899 c nhi\u7873 u n\u7907  hoa \u273 \'e0o nh\u432  v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e2u ra nhi\u7873 u hoa \u273 \'e0o nh\u432  th\u7871 , " Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7871 c h\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i, sau \u273 \'f3 g\u7909 c \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, "T\'f4i an \u7911 i con b\'e9 th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p tr\u7903  m\'ecnh l\u7853 t qua ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u259 n \u7903  ph\'eda ngo\'e0i b\'f2 xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i tr\u7889 n ra ban c\'f4ng, l\u7841 i g\u7885 i m\u7897 t cu\u7897 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho H\u7891  Tinh, c\u7889  \'fd h\u7841  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "H\u7891  t\u7927 , v\u7915 a r\u7891 i l\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n, ch\u7883  \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a? V\'e2ng... Ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i l\u7847 n n\'e0y em bi\u7871 t, em nh\u7899  ra c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'ean mang \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7875  ch\u7883  nh\'ecn th\u7917 ... Em c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 l\u7869  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i quan tr\u7885 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, con b\'e9 l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i duy nh\u7845 t trong su\u7889 t th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, cho t\u7899 i b\'e2y gi\u7901 , l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i quen chung c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i v\'e0 m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'fap \uc0\u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn s\u7855 c tr\u7901 i \'e2m u n\u7863 ng n\u7873  b\'ean ngo\'e0i, m\u7903  c\u7917 a ban c\'f4ng tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\u7841 nh ph\'eda ngo\'e0i gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\u7919  im l\u7863 ng leo l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, l\u7841 i tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p b\'f2 qua ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n b\'f2 v\'e0o trong y\'ean l\u7863 ng n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi "Ch\u7853 c" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng gi\u361  ch\u259 n b\u7885 c c\u7853 u l\u7841 i: "Sao l\u7841 i l\u7841 nh th\u7871  n\'e0y, \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7863 c th\'eam \u273 \u7891 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i kh\u7869  g\u7885 i t\'ean h\u7855 n: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u7911  ngon."\cb1 \
\cb3 May m\'e0 b\'ean m\'ecnh c\'f2n c\'f3 ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, may m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau sau khi tr\uc0\u7901 i s\'e1ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y li\u7873 n g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i h\u7865 n C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a \u273 i \u259 n, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n b\'e1o cho H\u7891  Tinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7857 m b\'ean c\u7841 nh nghe to\'e0n b\u7897  nh\u7919 ng g\'ec Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i "\u7914 , v\u7915 a x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n g\u7885 i em \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i gi\u7843 i s\u7847 u, tr\'e1nh cho trong l\'f2ng kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u" "H\u417 n n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\u7915  l\'e2u \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i mu\u7889 n c\'f9ng \u273 i \u259 n \u432 , v\u7851 n ch\u432 a h\u7865 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7847 n n\'e0o" "V\u7853 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, tr\u432 a nay g\u7863 p \u7903  nh\'e0 h\'e0ng 'Th\u7853 p t\'fay' ngo\'e0i c\u7893 ng \u273 \'f4ng" ...\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ch\u7901  c\u7853 u c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\u7899 i s\'e2u xa n\'f3i: "V\u7851 n r\u7845 t th\u432 \u417 ng hoa ti\u7871 c ng\u7885 c nh\u7881 , kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \'e3 b\u7843 o c\u7853 u t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t \'edt ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i c\'f4 ta th\'f4i sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi\'eam m\uc0\u7863 t n\'f3i: "T\'f4i \u273 i t\'ecm con b\'e9 th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 c\'f3 ch\'ednh s\u7921 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng kh\u7849 n c\u7847 u n\'f3i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\'f4i c\'f2n ph\u7843 i nh\u7901  c\u7853 u gi\'fap t\'f4i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i h\uc0\u7865 n con b\'e9 m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901  g\u7863 p, ch\u7855 c \u259 n m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e0 xong. N\u7871 u trong l\'fac \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i g\u7917 i cho c\u7853 u icon n\'e0y th\'ec c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c g\u7885 i cho t\'f4i gi\u7843  v\u7901  c\'f3 vi\u7879 c k\'eau t\'f4i \u273 i nh\'e9."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 c\u7853 u h\u7865 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ta \'e0? Th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 c\'f2n mu\u7889 n n\u7917 a \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng b\u7887  ch\u7841 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec n\u7871 u con b\'e9 c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , t\'f4i s\u7907  b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng c\'f3 can \u273 \u7843 m ki\'ean tr\'ec c\'f9ng con b\'e9 \u259 n xong b\u7919 a c\u417 m \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng n\'f3i cho c\uc0\u7853 u bi\u7871 t." C\u7853 u c\u7847 m m\u7897 t c\'e1nh tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  lay hai c\'e1i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng g\u7885 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng d\u7853 y bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng, "L\'e3o Di\u7879 p, xin c\u7853 u \u273 \u7845 y? C\u7853 u gi\'fap t\'f4i l\u7847 n n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? \u272 \u7875  b\'e1o \u273 \'e1p t\'f4i s\u7869  th\u7887 a m\'e3n m\u7897 t y\'eau c\u7847 u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac n\'e0o c\u361 ng m\u7897 t b\u7897  d\'e1ng thanh t\'e2m qu\u7843  d\u7909 c v\'f4 d\u7909 c v\'f4 c\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
