\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p, kinh ng\u7841 c \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7841 i sao Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i c\'f3 ID c\u7911 a "Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i"? Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869 ... C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i "Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i" th\u7853 t ? Ki\u7873 u th\'ea c\u7853 u y\'eau nh\u432  tr\'e2n b\u7843 o kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 y\'eau t\'e0 h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng s\u7901  s\u7901 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7921 a \u7903  t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o, b\'ecnh t\u297 nh m\'e0 bu\'f4ng m\u7855 t: "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng th\'edch C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i l\'e0 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i' . S\u7869  kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 h\u7843 o c\u7843 m v\u7899 i k\u7867  l\u7915 a \u273 \u7843 o gi\u7843  m\u7841 o m\'ecnh. Hu\u7889 ng chi c\'f4 ta c\u7889  \'fd gi\u7843  m\u7841 o th\'e2n ph\u7853 n 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i' ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n c\u7853 u, t\'e1m ch\'edn ph\u7847 n l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7891  x\u7845 u, t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean mu\u7889 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng tr\'e1nh xa c\'f4 ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\'f4ng ch\'fat ph\'e2n v\'e2n kh\'f4ng ch\'fat \'e1p l\u7921 c, ch\u7881  m\u7903  to hai m\u7855 t nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "... V\u7853 y t\u7841 i sao c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i t\'f4i? C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 c\'f4 ta gi\u7843  m\u7841 o..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n t\'f4i n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, gi\u7843 i th\'edch v\u7899 i c\u7853 u nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o? T\'f4i c\'f3 t\'e0i kho\u7843 n 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i', nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e2y c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 tr\u7897 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c; t\'f4i bi\u7871 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n x\u7843 y ra gi\u7919 a c\u7853 u v\'e0 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i' trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i, t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i b\'ed m\u7853 t, nh\u432 ng nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 t, c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n ph\'e1n \u273 o\'e1n ai l\'e0 th\u7853 t, ai l\'e0 gi\u7843  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o? M\u7845 u ch\u7889 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 dung m\u7841 o C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch v\'e0 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i' trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i g\u7847 n nh\u432  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'fac, v\u7853 y v\'e0o l\'fac \u273 \'f3, c\u7853 u s\u7869  ch\u7885 n tin t\u432 \u7903 ng t\'f4i, hay tin t\u432 \u7903 ng c\'f4 ta?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7915 a tr\u7847 m gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7915 a \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c lui v\u7873  sau, th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi l\u432 ng \u273 \u7909 ng v\'e0o t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi theo \u273 \'f3 \'e1p t\u7899 i, m\u7897 t tay ch\u7889 ng l\'ean c\u7917 a t\u7911  ph\'eda sau, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u: "... Hu\u7889 ng chi, t\'f4i ph\u7843 i n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \'e2y, r\u7857 ng n\u432 \u417 ng t\u7917  trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, th\u7853 t ra c\u7853 u n\'ean g\u7885 i l\'e0 t\u432 \u7899 ng c\'f4ng m\u7899 i ph\u7843 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i m\u7863 t k\u7873  qu\'e1 g\u7847 n, ch\'f3p m\u361 i g\u7847 n nh\u432  d\'e1n c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng h\u417 i th\u7903  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u417 i \u7903  tr\'ean m\u7863 t m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat m\uc0\u7845 t t\u7921  nhi\'ean h\u417 i quay quay m\u7863 t: "... V\u7853 y v\'ec sao b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u l\u7841 i nguy\u7879 n \'fd th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng tin c\'f4 ta, t\'f4i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9ng tay tr\'e1i c\u7847 m tay ph\u7843 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean tim c\u7853 u, ch\'f3p m\u361 i h\u7855 n c\u7885  l\'ean ch\'f3p m\u361 i c\u7853 u nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng tr\u432 \u7907 t, m\'f4i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\u417  \u273 \'e3ng l\u432 \u7899 t qua m\'f4i c\u7853 u, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u432  l\'f4ng v\u361  ph\u7845 t qua, v\u7915 a ch\u7841 m v\'e0o li\u7873 n r\u7901 i ra.\cb1 \
