\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e8 l\'ean tim m\'ecnh, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y, tim nh\u432  n\u7893 i tr\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u mu\u7889 n tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i m\u7853 p m\u7901  kh\'f4ng mi\'eau t\u7843  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\'fang \u273 \u7897 c n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ch\u7885 n c\'e2u kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p nh\u7845 t: "... L\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m gi\u7889 ng t\'f4i."\cb1 \
