\cb3 C\'f4 nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, gi\u417  m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p nh\u7887  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7871  t\u7841 o kh\'e9o l\'e9o tr\'ean tay l\'ean: "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\'e1m \u417 n anh \u273 \'e3 d\u7851 n em \u273 i \u259 n nh\'e9, \u273 \'fang l\'fac tr\u7903  v\u7873  em nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7917 a h\'e0ng b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t anh th\'edch n\'ean mua m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng, cho anh n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay ch\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 c\u7913 ng l\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t c\'e1nh tay du\u7895 i ra t\u7915  sau l\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7913 ng ngay sau c\u7853 u, nh\u7853 n l\u7845 y b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t: "C\u7843 m \u417 n. A Di\'ean \u273 ang chu\u7849 n b\u7883  thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 i g\u7863 p th\u7847 y gi\'e1o, kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p c\'f4 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c; c\'f3 mu\u7889 n v\'e0o ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat kh\'f4ng, t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  r\'f3t tr\'e0 tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n c\'f9ng c\'f4 m\u7897 t l\'e1t."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i n\'e0y n\'f3i c\u7921 c kh\'f4ng kh\'e1ch kh\'ed, tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c treo l\'ean. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7853 u th\'ec \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1 r\'f5 r\'e0ng, v\u7883  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i. Ngh\'eanh Chi trong l\'fac v\'f4 t\'ecnh ch\u7885 c gi\u7853 n "C\'f4 ta" th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao? Li\u7879 u c\'f3 l\'e0m h\u7841 i h\u7855 n hay kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch l\u7841 i ch\u7881  thu n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "N\u7871 u anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 vi\u7879 c th\'ec em kh\'f4ng qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y n\u7919 a, h\'f4m kh\'e1c g\u7863 p l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\uc0\u432 ng C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch nhanh ch\'f3ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, trong \u273 \u7847 u ph\'fac ch\u7889 c l\'f3e l\'ean r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u h\'ecnh \u7843 nh \'97\'97 C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch t\'ecm \u273 \u7871 n m\'ecnh, sau khi nghe n\'f3i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nhanh ch\'f3ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i; m\'ecnh g\u7885 i c\'f4 ta c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i \u259 n, c\'f4 ta nghe n\'f3i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng \u273 i s\u7869  ki\u7871 m c\u7899  t\u7915  ch\u7889 i...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'f3ng l\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang c\u7847 m b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch mang t\u7899 i n\'e9m v\'e0o th\'f9ng r\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Suy ngh\uc0\u297  ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c qu\u7843  kh\'f4ng sai, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t t\u7915  nguy\'ean nh\'e2n g\'ec, C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \'edch x\'e1c l\'e0 tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c khi H\u7891  Tinh gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, theo s\'e1t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  l\'e0 l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i ra ban c\'f4ng g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho H\u7891  Tinh. Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u h\u7887 i m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  b\u7843 n th\'e2n r\u7845 t nghi ho\u7863 c: "H\u7891  t\u7927 , ch\u7883  n\'f3i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, v\u7853 y th\'e2n ph\u7853 n kia c\u7911 a c\'f4 ta kia l\'e0 l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 c\'f3? Sao c\'f4 ta c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u432 \u7901 ng tuy\u7875 n v\'e0o, quang minh ch\'ednh \u273 \u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u h\u7887 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "N\u7871 u c\'f4 ta \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7909 y trang th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'e0 tr\u7897 n v\'e0o x\'e3 h\u7897 i lo\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  c\'f3 tr\u259 m ng\'e0n ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c m\u432 u t\'ednh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'e2n ph\u7853 n cho m\'ecnh. Im l\u7863 ng kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7841 o danh th\u7871  th\'e2n, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 b\'f3p m\'e9o h\u7891  s\u417  h\u7879  th\u7889 ng... Nhi\u7873 u v\'f4 s\u7889  k\u7875 , \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\'f4 ta lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng kh\'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915  trong ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u h\u7887 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\'f3 ph\u7847 n ng\'e2y th\u417 , kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i h\u417 i x\u7845 u h\u7893 , s\u7901  s\u7901  ch\'f3p m\u361 i, ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 \u273 em ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng chuy\u7879 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\'ecnh r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 quen bi\u7871 t C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch gi\u7843  m\u7841 o "Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i" , h\'f4m nay l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i l\'e0 "Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i" k\u7875  l\u7841 i cho H\u7891  Tinh. Tuy r\u7857 ng nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y nh\'ecn qua nh\u7887  nh\u7863 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng l\u432 u t\'e2m nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7901 , n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  cung c\u7845 p manh m\u7889 i cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh \u7903  \u273 \u7847 u b\'ean kia \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i n\'f3i: "\u272 \u7907 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7853 u n\'f3i l\'e0, th\u7913  kia bi\u7871 t m\u7885 i b\'ed m\u7853 t trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\'e0 b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng, ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh c\'f2n r\u7845 t gi\u7889 ng nh\'e2n v\u7853 t c\u7911 a b\u7841 n c\u7853 u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'e2ng." Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e1p. Sadako c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  b\'f2 ra t\u7915  TV, sau khi bi\u7871 t C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng th\'f4ng tin n\'e0y \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i h\'f3a th\'e0nh b\u7897  d\'e1ng t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921  "Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i" c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y k\u7923  l\u7841 . D\'f9 sao m\'ecnh v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c y\'eau t\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 "..." H\uc0\u7891  Tinh \u273 \u7847 u kia \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tr\u7847 m ng\'e2m th\u7853 t l\'e2u, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i t\u7915  t\u7915  m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng, "Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec, li\u7879 u c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u432 \u7899 ng suy ngh\u297  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\u259 n b\u7843 n \u273 \'e3 sai hay kh\'f4ng? Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i 'C\'f4 ta' theo d\'f5i c\u7853 u cho n\'ean c\u7889  \'fd gi\u7843  m\u7841 o 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i' tuy th\'e2n thi\u7871 t v\u7899 i c\u7853 u nh\u432 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7901 i; m\'e0 l\'e0 v\'ec 'C\'f4 ta' v\u7889 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i " n\'ean m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  v\u7915 a xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh m\u7909 c ti\'eau \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t t\u7899 i phu qu\'e2n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'e0 c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7891  t\u7927 , ch\u7883  \u273 ang n\'f3i c\'e1i g\'ec? Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i r\u7845 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7853 u \u7845 y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng g\u7841 t em, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng g\u7841 t em trong chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, t\'f4i n\'f3i l\'e0, C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\'f3 kha\u777  n\u259 ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 nh\'e2n v\u7853 t 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i " m\'e0 b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u t\u7841 o ra trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i kia."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c s\u7919 ng s\u7901 .\cb1 \
