\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m nh\'e2n v\u7853 t trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i c\u7911 a b\u7841 n c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i b\u7841 n, l\'e0m sao b\u7841 n bi\u7871 t n\'f3 l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u7919  li\u7879 u \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n, hay l\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  mu\u7889 n c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i b\u7841 n?\cb1 \
