\cb3 "... Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7843 i th\'edch, s\u7903  d\u297  'C\'f4 ta' m\u7863 c d\'f9 c\'f3 h\u7845 p thu t\'e0 kh\'ed h\'f3a th\'e0nh b\u7843 n h\'ecnh y\'eau t\'e0, nh\u432 ng trong hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7921 c th\u7875 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\'f9ng t\'e0 kh\'ed t\u7841 m th\u7901 i ng\u432 ng ra m\u7897 t th\'e2n th\u7875 , c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7871  t\u7841 o m\u7897 t k\'fd th\u7875  cho ch\'ednh m\'ecnh tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac t\'e0 kh\'ed tan h\u7871 t. Tr\'e1ch kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c 'C\'f4 ta' g\u7845 p g\'e1p nh\u432  v\u7853 y." H\u7891  Tinh \u7903  b\'ean kia \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i, "Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\u361 ng l\u7841 , b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u \u273 i \u273 \'e2u l\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  th\u7913  t\'e0 kh\'ed n\'e0y d\'ednh v\'e0o ho\'e0nh h\'e0nh ngang ng\u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7853 m ch\'ed tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p h\'f3a th\'e0nh ma qu\u7927 !"\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e2n v\uc0\u7853 t tr\'f2 ch\u417 i tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7917  ch\u7881  gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 i\'eau kh\u7855 c l\u7841 i c\'e0ng th\'eam sinh \u273 \u7897 ng, nh\u432 ng ch\'fang kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i th\u7871  gi\u7899 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i, theo l\'fd m\'e0 n\'f3i t\u7927  l\u7879  ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i t\'e0 th\u7853 t ra kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\'edch giao ti\u7871 p, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\'edch c\'e1c ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng gi\u7843 i tr\'ed xung quanh, \u273 \u7841 i \u273 a s\u7889  th\u7901 i gian kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec l\'e0 \u7903  nh\'e0, l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p x\'fac \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i t\'e0 kh\'ed n\u7863 ng...\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\u7853 u h\u417 i ng\u7849 n ra, \u7903  nh\'e0... \u7903  nh\'e0 m\'e0 n\'f3i, b\'e0 tr\u7867  \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i c\u259 n nh\'e0 Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\u7915 ng x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n, t\u7915 ng b\u7883  b\'e0i b\u7889  t\u7909  t\'e0 tr\u7853 n, nghe v\'e0o tai c\'f2n gi\u7889 ng t\'e0 linh c\u7921 c k\u7923  m\u7841 nh. N\u7871 u l\u7901 i b\'e0 tr\u7867  n\'f3i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 s\u7921  th\u7853 t, tuy r\u7857 ng theo l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i h\u7855 n \u7903  \u273 \'f3 ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7913  ba t\u7891 n t\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng ph\u7843 i n\'f3i l\'e0, t\'e0 kh\'ed \u7903  ch\u7895  m\'ecnh kia \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1 m\u7841 nh r\u7891 i, cho d\'f9 th\u7913  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i \u273 i, ch\u7881  s\u7907  c\u361 ng s\u7869  l\u432 u l\u7841 i t\'e0 kh\'ed ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\uc0\u7875  chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y cho H\u7891  Tinh, H\u7891  Tinh l\u7849 m b\u7849 m "Ch\u7859 ng tr\'e1ch", l\u7841 i d\u7863 n d\'f2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7845 y c\'e2u m\u7899 i c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng, n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\'f4i mu\u7889 n xin c\u7853 u m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c, c\u7853 u x\'f3a nh\'e2n v\u7853 t Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i kia \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? T\'f4i l\u7845 y Di\u7879 p tam khi\u7871 m \u273 \u7873 n cho c\u7853 u." L\'fac \u7845 y hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 b\u7887  ra kh\'f4ng \'edt th\u7901 i gian v\'e0 ti\u7873 n b\u7841 c cho tr\'f2 ch\u417 i, nh\'e2n v\u7853 t Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i n\'e0y hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u361 ng tr\u7883  gi\'e1 kh\'f4ng \'edt ti\u7873 n. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 c\u7911 a chung c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, s\'e0n s\'e0n nhau, s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh tr\'ecnh \u273 \u7897  hai nh\'e2n v\u7853 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch l\u7855 m, \u273 \u432 a "Di\u7879 p tam khi\u7871 m" cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng th\'edch h\u7907 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i, t\'f4i n\'f3i m\u7853 t kh\u7849 u cho c\u7853 u, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i t\'f4i c\u361 ng \u273 \u7875  \u7903  b\'ean kia, t\u7921  c\u7853 u x\'f3a \u273 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i nguy\'ean nh\'e2n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng c\u7853 u, ngh\u297  ngh\u297  l\u7841 i b\u7893  sung, "Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u nh\u432  th\u7871  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n n\u7907  'Di\u7879 p tam khi\u7871 m" m\u7897 t n\u432 \u417 ng t\u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  cho l\'e0 c\'e2u cu\u7889 i h\u7855 n \u273 ang n\'f3i \u273 \'f9a, c\'e1m \u417 n xong v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ng\u7891 i v\'e0o ch\u7895  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi x\'f3a nh\'e2n v\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Suy \uc0\u273 o\'e1n c\u7911 a H\u7891  Tinh ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n ch\'ednh x\'e1c, b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u x\'f3a nh\'e2n v\u7853 t "Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i" n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u7855 t s\u7869  sinh ra \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng v\u7899 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, nh\u432 ng chung quy c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m y\u7871 u b\u7899 t s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh c\u7911 a C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch. Hu\u7889 ng chi b\'e2y gi\u7901  s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a nh\'e2n v\u7853 t n\'e0y b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0m c\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, khi\u7871 n l\'f2ng c\u7853 u ch\'e1n gh\'e9t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7921 a ch\u7885 n \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  x\'f3a b\u7887  nh\'e2n v\u7853 t, sau m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m ng\'e0y b\u7843 o v\u7879  nh\'e2n v\u7853 t n\'e0y s\u7869  b\u7883  x\'f3a, sau ba m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y b\u7843 o v\u7879  s\u7869  v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\'e3n ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i, \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, v\u7915 a quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i ch\u7907 t ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7871  nh\u432 ng \u273 ang thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0m g\'ec th\u7871 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Thu d\uc0\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c, \u273 \'eam nay v\u7873  nh\'e0 \u7903 ." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7841 m d\u7915 ng thao t\'e1c tr\'ean tay, r\u7845 t t\u7921  nhi\'ean \u273 \'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng trong nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 t\'e0 kh\'ed r\u7845 t \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 trong t\'ecnh h\'ecnh nguy c\u7845 p tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y, theo s\'e1t h\u7855 n v\u7851 n c\u7913  quan tr\u7885 ng h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n m\'ecnh thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c mu\u7889 n mang \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7859 ng l\u432 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "C\u7853 u l\u7841 i l\'e0m g\'ec v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i v\'f4 c\'f9ng t\u7921  nhi\'ean tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "Thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c c\'f9ng v\u7873  nh\'e0 v\u7899 i c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7915 ng d\u7885 n n\u7919 a, h\'f4m nay kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh mang c\u7853 u theo."\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7843 ?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7907 n tr\'f2n m\u7855 t nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tin.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i c\'e1i g\'ec? H\'f4m nay h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng mang m\'ecnh \u273 i c\'f9ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \u7889 ng qu\u7847 n \'e1o s\'e1ch v\u7903  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 \u7875  \u7903  nh\'e0 h\u7855 n, ngay trong t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\u7899 i t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 n g\u7847 n \u273 \u7871 n c\u7853 u hai b\u432 \u7899 c, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "... A Di\'ean, n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u7853 u c\'f3 hi\u7875 u kh\'f4ng? Con ng\u432 \u7901 i ai c\u361 ng c\'f3 nhu c\u7847 u, c\u7853 u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng n\'f3i r\'f5, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'fd t\u7913  C\u7910 A \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t c\u7853 u trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t tr\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng, n\'f3ng \u273 \u7871 n ph\'e1t nhi\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 g\'e2y th\'eam phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e0 kh\'f4ng t\u7921  bi\u7871 t, th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i m\u7863 t d\'e0y m\'e0y d\u7841 n c\u7913  d\'ednh l\u7845 y h\u7855 n khi\u7871 n h\u7855 n gh\'e9t b\u7887 , n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m ch\u7883 u kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i r\u7891 i, h\'f4m nay m\u7899 i n\'f3i ra th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u nh\u432  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  ng\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c b\'e1m l\u7845 y h\u7855 n, nh\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  t\'ecnh h\'ecnh \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, ch\u7881  c\'f3 theo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i an to\'e0n nh\u7845 t, c\u361 ng an t\'e2m nh\u7845 t. C\u7853 u c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng c\u7889  g\u7855 ng n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u cho t\'f4i v\u7873  c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u273 i, t\'f4i s\u7869  chuy\u7875 n ph\'f2ng, t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  lau nh\'e0 gi\u7863 t qu\u7847 n \'e1o... C\u7853 u \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i theo c\u7853 u l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\u7847 n n\'e0y t\'f4i cam \u273 oan s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y c\u7853 u." Cho d\'f9 l\'e0 tr\u7903  l\u7841 i c\u259 n ph\'f2ng hai l\u7847 n \u273 \u7909 ng qu\u7927  kia c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c." Kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n t\u7915  ch\u7889 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nhi\uc0\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\'f4i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, l\u7847 n n\'e0y \u273 \'fang l\'fac mu\u7889 n th\u7917  \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c gi\'fap t\'f4i gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t. C\'f3 c\u7853 u \u7903  \u273 \'f3, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ti\u7879 n mang ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 l\u7841 i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh t\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y mu\u7889 n l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n lo\u7841 i n\'e0y h\u7843 ! Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n r\'f5 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7853 t s\u7921  mu\u7889 n v\u7853 y hay l\'e0 c\u7889  \'fd n\'f3i l\u7901 i n\'e0y l\u7915 a g\u7841 t c\u7853 u, ch\'ednh l\'e0 kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n c\u7853 u v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i g\uc0\u7885 i l\'e0 "G\u7847 n th\'ec nh\u7901 n xa th\'ec o\'e1n", Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m x\u432 ng l\'e0 qu\'e2n t\u7917 . L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u qu\'e1 t\u7889 t, h\'f4m nay \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t b\u7845 t ng\u7901  b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ki\u7871 m \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i c\u7899  kh\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\u7845 y c\u7899  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c sinh ra v\'e0i ph\u7847 n o\'e1n h\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u c\'f3 ch\'fat gi\u7853 n d\u7895 i n\'f3i: "V\u7853 y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, t\'f4i gi\'fap c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u432 a?" C\u7853 u n\'f3i l\u7901 i n\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u \'f3c ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng suy ngh\u297 , \u273 \u7863 t \u7903  tr\'ean th\'e2n ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c s\u7869  ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7903  \u273 \u7847 u c\'e3i nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, h\u7855 n "\'c0" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c tho\u7843 i m\'e1i nh\'e0n nh\'e3 thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  b\u7887  m\u7863 c \u7903  \u273 \'f3, \u273 ang nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7915 a \u273 \u7883 nh l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, ch\u7907 t nghe Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7843 n nhi\'ean n\'f3i: "Sao c\u7853 u c\'f2n ch\u432 a d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "D\uc0\u7885 n c\'e1i g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "D\uc0\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  c\'f9ng t\'f4i v\u7873  nh\'e0." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i y\'ean l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, "L\u7901 i \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u t\'f4i ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n, c\u7853 u c\'f9ng t\'f4i v\u7873  nh\'e0, c\u7853 u gi\'fap t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean cho\'e1ng v\'e1ng h\u7891  \u273 \u7891  n\u7857 m \u7903  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n l\u7901 i h\u7913 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ch\u7881  l\'e0 gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  ki\u7875 u \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n nh\u7845 t, h\u417 n n\u7919 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f2n \u273 em chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1ch \u273 \u417 n ph\u432 \u417 ng \u7903  \u273 \'fat l\'f3t ch\u7911  nh\'e0 n\'e0y bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh h\u7843 o h\u7919 u gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  l\u7851 n nhau, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n x\u7845 u h\u7893  \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f4ng m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac sau c\'f9ng v\u7851 n c\'f3 ph\u7847 n m\u7845 t kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871 , th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c t\'ecnh t\u7921  kh\'f3 n\'e9n nh\u7845 t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ph\u7911  ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i h\'f4n c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t n\u7909  h\'f4n s\'e2u.\cb1 \
