\cb3 V\'ed d\uc0\u7909  nh\u432  "B\'e0 x\'e3, t\u7899 i \u259 n c\u417 m" "B\'e0 x\'e3, n\'ean \u273 i ng\u7911  r\u7891 i" "B\'e0 x\'e3, l\'e0m phi\u7873 n b\'e0 x\'e3 gi\u7863 t qu\u7847 n \'e1o cho \'f4ng x\'e3 r\u7891 i" ... Nhi\u7873 u kh\'f4ng k\u7875  xi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 X\uc0\u7845 u xa x\u7845 u xa.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  n\u7909  h\'f4n ph\u7847 n ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3, tuy r\u7857 ng th\u7901 i gian Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e8 c\u7853 u h\'f4n kh\'f4ng ng\u7855 n, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 v\'f4 c\'f9ng d\u7877  l\'fd gi\u7843 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7841 i lo\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \'f3, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \'fd lo\u7841 n t\'ecnh m\'ea, n\'f3i th\u7853 t... c\u7853 u c\u361 ng r\u7845 t mu\u7889 n h\'f4n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi...\cb1 \
\cb3 Lo\uc0\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y h\'ecnh nh\u432  s\u7869  nghi\u7879 n, t\u7915  ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 sau khi ph\'e1 gi\u7899 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i l\'f4i k\'e9o c\u7853 u r\u7845 t kh\u7855 c ch\u7871  c\u7885  x\'e1t ba b\u7889 n l\u7847 n, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e8 c\u7853 u h\'f4n c\u7853 u, th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi c\u7853 u m\u7879 t m\u7887 i l\u7841 i \'f4m c\u7853 u ng\u7911  chung trong m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c m\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'edch, th\uc0\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 c\'f3 ch\'fat m\'ea luy\u7871 n lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c d\'ednh s\'e1t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'e0y, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i tr\u7855 ng ra, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng t\u7915  ch\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qua b\uc0\u7843 y ng\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i H\u7891  Tinh g\u7885 i t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 b\uc0\u7841 n h\u7885 c l\'e3o Vi\'ean, s\u432  \u273 \u7879  H\u7891  Tinh \'96 Ti\u7875 u An c\u361 ng c\'f3 li\'ean l\u7841 c, t\u7915  ch\u7895  c\u7853 u ta bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  sau ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3, g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t l\'e0 v\'e0o ban \u273 \'eam H\u7891  Tinh \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  ngh\u7881  theo s\'e1t C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, ban ng\'e0y ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i hai ba ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c nghi\'ean c\u7913 u ghi ch\'e9p trong s\'e1ch c\u7893  ho\u7863 c t\u432  li\u7879 u li\'ean quan \u273 \u7875  t\'ecm nh\u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, m\u7897 t l\u7847 n h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng di\u7879 t tr\u7915  ho\'e0n to\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'e0 v\uc0\u7853 t trong tay d\'ednh \u273 \u7847 y m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, d\'f9 l\'e0 H\u7891  Tinh c\u361 ng kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  cam \u273 oan s\u7869  d\u7877  d\'e0ng h\'e0ng ph\u7909 c, m\'e0 m\u7897 t khi \u273 \'e1nh r\u7855 n \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7887 , n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u417  h\u7897 i h\u7841  th\u7911 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng gi\u7871 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng t\u7915 ng xem phim kinh d\u7883  nh\u432  th\u7871 , nh\'e2n v\u7853 t ch\'ednh, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7843  \u273 \u7841 o s\u297  h\'f2a th\u432 \u7907 ng thu\u7853 t s\u297  cao nh\'e2n trong phim to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7871 t, m\'e0 con qu\u7927  th\'ec tho\u7843 i m\'e1i s\u7889 ng t\u7899 i cu\u7889 i, quan s\'e1t v\'e0 ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i con m\u7891 i ti\u7871 p theo.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng li\'ean h\u7879  H\u7891  Tinh, s\u7907  qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7883 , ch\u7881  \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh nghe ng\'f3ng m\u7897 t \'edt tin t\u7913 c t\u7915  ch\u7895  Ti\u7875 u An.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i b\uc0\u7883  c\'f4 ta ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n r\u7891 i." \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 c\'e2u n\'f3i \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7911 a H\u7891  Tinh, thanh \'e2m c\'f3 ch\'fat h\u7851 ng, "C\'f4 ta r\u7845 t x\u7843 o tr\'e1, c\'f4 ta \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u7845 u v\u7871 t c\u7911 a t\'f4i, l\u7841 i gi\u7843  v\u7901  nh\u432  ch\u432 a ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n. Sau \u273 \'f3... h\'f4m nay th\u7915 a c\u417  ra tay v\u7899 i A S\'eanh."\cb1 \
\cb3 "A S\'eanh hi\uc0\u7879 n gi\u7901  \u7903  v\'e0o t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng nguy c\u7845 p, l\'fac n\'e0y t\'f4i ph\u7843 i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng c\u7913 u n\'f3... Th\u7853 t xin l\u7895 i, \'edt nh\u7845 t trong n\u259 m ng\'e0y t\u7899 i t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o lo chuy\u7879 n C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch b\'ean \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 A S\'eanh ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t con h\u7891  ly nh\u7887 , cho d\'f9 c\'f3 ch\'fat linh t\'ednh v\'e0 b\u7843 n l\u297 nh \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng \u273 \'e1nh kh\'f4ng l\u7841 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch. C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a n\'f3, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7913 ng minh m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n, c\'f4 ta c\u7889  \'fd mu\u7889 n d\'f9ng vi\u7879 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  t\'e1ch H\u7891  Tinh \u273 i \'97\'97 c\'f4 ta \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra H\u7891  Tinh, H\u7891  Tinh b\'e1m theo qu\'e1 s\'e1t khi\u7871 n c\'f4 ta kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u417  h\u7897 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7841  th\u7911 , m\'e0 c\'f4 ta l\u7841 i \u273 \u7907 i kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bi\uc0\u7871 t r\'f5 \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 c\u7841 m b\u7851 y, bi\u7871 t r\'f5 \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 k\u7871  \u273 i\u7879 u h\u7893  ly s\u417 n, H\u7891  Tinh c\u361 ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i \u273 i theo h\u432 \u7899 ng m\'e0 C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch mu\u7889 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  \u7903  trong m\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c kh\'f3 m\'e0 hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u432 ng trong m\u7855 t H\u7891  Tinh, A S\'eanh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7911 a ch\u7883 . D\'f9 bi\u7871 t n\u7871 u m\'ecnh t\'e1ch kh\u7887 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, c\'f4 ta s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng \u273 i h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, ch\u7883  c\u361 ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i c\u7913 u ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh tr\u432 \u7899 c. M\u7863 c d\'f9 ch\u7883  l\'e0 thu\u7853 t s\u297  \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng. nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Xin l\uc0\u7895 i." H\u7891  Tinh th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng sao \uc0\u273 \'e2u, nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y em s\u7869  c\u7849 n th\u7853 n." C\u7853 u hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'fd t\u7913  c\'e2u "Xin l\u7895 i" kia c\u7911 a H\u7891  Tinh, c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe H\u7891  Tinh k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng tr\u7843 i qua, \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7875 u h\u7891  ly kia c\'f3 \'fd ngh\u297 a nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o v\u7899 i ch\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f2n n\uc0\u7919 a, H\u7891  t\u7927 , ngo\'e0i ch\u7883  ra c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng \u273 \u7841 o s\u297  thu\u7853 t s\u297  h\'f2a th\u432 \u7907 ng kh\'e1c \u273 ang lo chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng?" Tuy r\u7857 ng ngh\u7873  n\'e0y c\'e1ch xa cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\u432 ng theo l\'fd m\'e0 n\'f3i H\u7891  Tinh c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7891 ng h\'e0nh, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh chi\u7871 n \u273 \u7845 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ph\uc0\u7843 i, " H\u7891  Tinh n\'f3i, "Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u th\u7913  cho t\'f4i n\'f3i th\u7859 ng, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i tham d\u7921  trong chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t ai c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng c\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f2n m\uc0\u7897 t vi\u7879 c, Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec, c\u7853 u n\'f3i c\u7853 u l\u226 \u769 y c\'f4 ta l\'e0m v\u7907  trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i, l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec? Qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh c\u7909  th\u7875  l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t v\'ec sao ch\u7883  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean h\u7887 i c\'e2u n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n k\u7875  l\u7841 i qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh th\'e0nh h\'f4n trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n k\u7929  c\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 b\'e1i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, h\'e0nh l\u7877 , l\u7853 p l\u7901 i th\u7873 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'e2ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y nguy r\u7891 i..." Gi\u7885 ng H\u7891  Tinh c\'f3 ch\'fat ng\u432 ng tr\u7885 ng, "T\'f4i bi\u7871 t ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng coi nh\u7919 ng quan h\u7879  tr\'ean m\u7841 ng n\'e0y l\'e0 th\u7853 t, nh\u432 ng nghi th\u7913 c l\'e0 nghi th\u7913 c, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n nghi l\u7877  th\'e0nh h\'f4n, \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'ednh l\'e0 v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng th\uc0\u7875  n\'e0o," Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f3 tin, "D\'f9 c\'f3 l\'e0 th\u7871 , th\'ec c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 em v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\'ednh l\'e0 v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng gi\uc0\u7889 ng nhau, n\u7871 u nh\'e2n v\u7853 t kia ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 o c\u7909  do b\u7841 n c\u7853 u \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n, v\u7853 y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean quan h\u7879  h\'f4n nh\'e2n ch\u7881  th\'e0nh l\u7853 p gi\u7919 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e1c c\u7853 u; nh\u432 ng hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  th\u7913  kia \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh t\'e0 v\u7853 t c\'f3 linh h\u7891 n, t\u7847 ng quan h\u7879  h\'f4n nh\'e2n n\'e0y \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i th\'e0nh l\u7853 p ngay gi\u7919 a c\u7853 u v\'e0 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 . N\u417 i \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng lu\u7853 n m\u7897 t v\u7907  m\u7897 t ch\u7891 ng hay kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p tr\'f9ng h\'f4n, nghi th\u7913 c \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh, quan h\u7879  li\u7873 n k\'fd k\u7871 t xong."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e1ng lo nh\u7845 t kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 vi\u7879 c n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean, h\'f4m qua t\'f4i v\u7915 a tra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, th\u7913  kia n\u7871 u mu\u7889 n l\'e0m cho m\'ecnh m\u7897 t b\u7897  k\'fd th\u7875  th\'edch h\u7907 p nh\u7845 t, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i c\u7847 n hai th\u7913  \'97\'97m\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n, v\'e0 tim ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tim? Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean b\u7883  gi\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 b\u7883 , \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  m\'f3c tim sao..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng sai, tim l\'e0 ngu\uc0\u7891 n g\u7889 c s\u7921  s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a con ng\u432 \u7901 i. N\u7871 u mu\u7889 n duy tr\'ec s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a k\'fd th\u7875  kh\'f4ng tr\u7885 n v\u7865 n kia, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ban s\u417  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i mang m\u7897 t tr\'e1i tim, sau \u273 \'f3 ch\u7901  l\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\'e1i tim quan tr\u7885 ng nh\u7845 t v\'e0o tay th\'ec s\u7869  thay v\'e0o."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\'f4 ta l\'e0 ma qu\u7927  \u432 ? C\'f4 ta t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u7903  \u273 \'e2u, l\u7841 i t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n \u7903  \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 m\u417  h\u7891  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, "Ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau" kia, t\'e1m ch\'edn ph\u7847 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 ch\u7881  m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... C\uc0\u7853 u ch\'ednh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a 'C\'f4 ta', Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh th\'e2n v\u7899 i c\'f4 ta, cha m\u7865  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\u361 ng li\u7873 n tr\u7903  th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7911 a c\'f4 ta..."\cb1 \
\cb3 'C\'f4 ta' c\'f2n c\uc0\u7847 n hai th\u7913 , m\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n, tim ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh th\'e2n v\u7899 i c\'f4 ta, cha m\u7865  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7911 a c\'f4 ta.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Hai c\'e2u n\'f3i n\'e0y gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\'faa t\u7841 , t\u7915 ng c\'e1i t\u7915 ng c\'e1i li\'ean t\u7909 c n\u7879 n v\'e0o l\'f2ng c\u7853 u, kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng d\u7897 i l\'ean ti\u7871 ng vang.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i trong tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean "C\u7841 ch" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng n\'e0y l\'e0m b\u7915 ng t\u7881 nh, l\u7841 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m xu\u7889 ng, h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng run run nh\u7863 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i l\'ean, kh\'f4ng c\u7843  \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, c\u7913  t\u432  th\u7871  nh\u432  v\u7853 y run r\u7849 y ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c g\u7885 i l\u7841 i cho H\u7891  Tinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7891  t\u7927 , em xin ch\u7883 , em xin ch\u7883 ... c\u7913 u ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 c\u7911 a em, c\u7913 u ba m\u7865  em..." H\'e0m r\u259 ng c\u7853 u run l\'ean, gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i run kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh b\'ean kia im l\u7863 ng th\u7853 t l\'e2u, m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u sau m\u7899 i n\'f3i: "Xin l\u7895 i, t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o. G\u7847 n nh\'e0 c\u7853 u n\u7871 u c\'f3 linh v\u7853 t b\u7843 o \u273 \u7883 a g\'ec, v\u7853 y n\'ean b\u7843 o cha m\u7865  c\u7853 u t\u7841 m th\u7901 i tr\'e1nh \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'ean kia truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n \'e2m thanh "t\'edt t\'edt", nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n t\'ea li\u7879 t ng\u7891 i d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. C\u7853 u ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i, c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y s\u7869  b\u7903 i ch\'ednh m\'ecnh m\'e0 mang h\u7885 a \u273 \u7871 n cho cha m\u7865 , g\'e2y h\u7885 a cho ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f2n l\'e0 h\uc0\u7885 a do ma qu\u7927  nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 \u7847 u \'f3c c\u7853 u r\u7889 i lo\u7841 n, ng\u7891 i d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7863 t v\'e9 v\u7873  nh\'e0, m\'e1y bay ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7863 t chuy\u7871 n bay ng\'e0y mai, xe l\u7917 a ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i v\u7851 n c\'f2n chuy\u7871 n bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i\'97\'97 b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i v\u7873  nh\'e0 g\u7863 p cha m\u7865 . C\u7853 u ph\u7843 i b\u7843 o v\u7879  h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean mua v\'e9 xong v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e3 v\'e0o nh\'e0 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u li\u7873 n h\'f4: "A Di\'ean, c\u7853 u l\'e0m g\'ec th\u7871 ? C\u7853 u mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7915 ng \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "T\'f4i ph\u7843 i v\u7873  nh\'e0 m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n, Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y qua c\u7843 m \u417 n c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 chi\u7871 u c\u7889  t\'f4i, c\'f3 th\u7875  g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u th\u7853 t t\u7889 t." C\u7853 u gi\u7853 t nh\u7865  kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng, mu\u7889 n n\u7903  m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u7913 c ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u s\u7907 , c\u7853 u qu\'e1 s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, kho\'e1t tay tr\'e1i l\'ean vai ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean, x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec? N\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7841 i th\'ec \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i v\u7873  c\'f9ng c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, trong l\'f2ng tho\'e1ng c\'e1i l\u7841 i d\'e2ng l\'ean m\u7897 t ch\'fat hy v\u7885 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch lu\'f4n tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, mang Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7873  nh\'e0 tr\'e1nh m\u7845 y ng\'e0y H\u7891  Tinh kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u c\'f3 th\u7875  k\'e9o d\'e0i qua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ki\u7871 p n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7855 n d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch th\u7853 t v\u7845 t v\u7843  t\'e1ch H\u7891  Tinh ra, ch\'f3 c\'f9ng r\u7913 t gi\u7853 u, nh\u432  v\u7853 y ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i li\u7879 u c\'f3 l\'e0m h\u7841 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng m\u7845 t m\u7841 ng hay kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f4i c\uc0\u7853 u ng\u7853 p ng\u7915 ng, h\u417 i run run, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i n\'f3i kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i, m\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh n\u7863 n ra m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "... L\u7847 n n\'e0y s\u7869  r\u7845 t nguy hi\u7875 m, r\u7845 t nguy hi\u7875 m, c\'f3 t\'e0 y\'eau mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 c\u7911 a t\'f4i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i c\u7853 u n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t n\u7917 a l\u7841 i b\u7883  ng\u259 n l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u417 i nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u h\u7841  th\u7845 p ng\u432 \u7901 i, cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t n\u7909  h\'f4n r\u7845 t nh\u7865 . L\'e0nh l\u7841 nh, r\u417 i tr\'ean m\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  bi\u7871 t ng\'e2y ng\u7889 c ng\u7917 a \u273 \u7847 u tr\u7907 n tr\'f2n m\u7855 t nh\'ecn h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9ng ng\'f3n tr\u7887  tay ph\u7843 i ch\u7841 m nh\u7865  l\'ean m\'f4i c\u7853 u, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "Ngoan, \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3i nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y. Ch\'fang ta \u273 \'e3 b\'e1i thi\'ean \u273 \u7883 a, c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n t\u432 \u7899 ng c\'f4ng \u273 i c\'f9ng v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, v\u7853 y g\u7885 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng '\'d4ng x\'e3' \u273 i ."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e3 l\'fac n\'e0o r\u7891 i, v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 \'f9a gi\u7905 n th\u7871  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u \u273 en c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , r\u7891 i l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'e2m \'fd ch\'e2n ch\'ednh c\u7911 a h\u7855 n trong \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng c\'f3 ch\'fat ngh\uc0\u7865 n, c\'f3 ch\'fat \u273 \'e1nh tr\u7889 ng h\'f2 reo. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng n\'f3i kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ch\u7881  ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng d\u7921 a qua \'f4m l\u7845 y eo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng k\'eau m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng "Ngh\'eanh Chi" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 v\'e0o th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'ean ti\u7871 ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, l\u7841 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai h\u7855 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  n\u7881  non g\u7885 i ra hai ch\u7919  kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... \'d4ng x\'e3."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n r\u7845 t x\u7845 u h\u7893 , m\u7863 t tho\'e1ng c\'e1i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3ng nh\u432  thi\'eau \u273 \u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng... K\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 quen bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, h\'f4n h\'f4n l\'ean tai c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
