\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \u7913 ng ra quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh, b\u7843 o Tr\'ec Di\'ean ho\'e0n l\u7841 i v\'e9, c\'f9ng h\u7855 n l\'e1i xe v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ga m\u7845 t g\u7847 n m\u7897 t gi\u7901  \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, t\'ednh th\'eam c\u7843  n\u7917 a ti\u7871 ng ch\u7901  xe, th\u7901 i gian \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  H c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7855 n, ch\u7859 ng b\u7857 ng tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p l\'e1i xe \u273 i cao t\u7889 c thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n mau l\u7865  h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7859 ng khi \u273 \u7871 n ng\u7891 i tr\'ean xe th\u7855 t d\'e2y an to\'e0n r\u7891 i c\u361 ng ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t c\'e2u ho\'e0n ch\u7881 nh v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'e2ng m\u7855 t nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, v\'e0nh tai c\'f2n h\u417 i h\u7891 ng h\u7891 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng xe, m\u7855 t nh\'ecn ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3i: "Sao l\u7841 i x\u7845 u h\u7893 , kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i tr\u432 \u7899 c kia trong game t\'f4i c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng g\u7885 i c\u7853 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe h\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i th\u7871  m\u7863 t l\u7841 i h\u417 i n\'f3ng l\'ean: "... \u272 \u7915 ng n\'f3i n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7917 a h\'e0ng x\u259 ng g\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7893  th\'eam x\u259 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 d\u7921 a theo h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n ch\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e1i xe th\u7859 ng m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  H, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng t\u7899 i khi hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'ec \u273 \'e3 h\u417 n ch\'edn gi\u7901  t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac v\uc0\u7915 a xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\u7873  nh\'e0, n\'f3i tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881 , c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n m\u7897 t b\u7841 n h\u7885 c v\u7873  ch\u417 i hai ng\'e0y, c\u361 ng d\u7863 n d\'f2 b\u7885 n h\u7885  g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng an to\'e0n, k\'eau h\u7885  kh\'f4ng n\'ean t\'f9y ti\u7879 n m\u7903  c\u7917 a cho ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 , ban \u273 \'eam c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cha m\uc0\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n r\u7845 t ti\u7871 n b\u7897 , tr\u432 \u7899 c kia Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng mang l\'e3o Vi\'ean v\'e0 c\'e1c b\u7841 n h\u7885 c \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  H ch\u417 i, cho n\'ean th\u7853 t ra c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y k\u7923  l\u7841 , ch\u7881  th\u7847 m nghi ho\u7863 c tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u cho ngh\u7881  d\u7883 p g\'ec, sao l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ngay th\u7871  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \'e3 th\'f4ng b\'e1o t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a g\'f5 c\u7917 a n\'f3i "Con v\u7873  r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y", Tr\'ec Chung Vi\u7877 n \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i m\u7903  c\u7917 a, nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh \u273 \'f3n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0o, mang \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7887  v\'e0o ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, sau \u273 \'f3 g\u7885 i c\u7843  hai ra ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch ng\u7891 i. M\u7865  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, L\u432 u Ph\u432 \u7907 ng O\'e1nh t\u7913 c th\'ec b\u432 ng hoa qu\u7843  \u273 \'e3 g\u7885 t s\u7861 n l\'ean, l\u7841 i l\u7845 y n\u432 \u7899 c cho c\u7843  hai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Chung Vi\uc0\u7877 n nh\'ecn con trai n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, h\'f4m nay kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\'e0y l\u7877 , con \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 ngh\u7881  d\u7883 p g\'ec th\u7871 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u7845 p \'fang n\'f3i kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i, c\u7853 u ch\'ednh l\'e0 thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng b\u7883 a ra, tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881 . Nh\u432 ng d\u7921 a theo t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7911 a cha m\u7865 , m\u7863 c k\u7879  con l\'e0 h\u7885 c sinh ti\u7875 u h\u7885 c hay l\'e0 nghi\'ean c\u7913 u sinh, tr\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng cho ngh\u7881  th\'ec n\'ean th\'e0nh th\'e0nh th\u7853 t th\u7853 t \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec m\'e0 tr\u7889 n h\u7885 c v\u7873  nh\'e0 th\'ec l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f3 gi\u7843 i th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1p: "D\u7841  ch\'fa, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 ngh\u7881  k\u7927  ni\u7879 m ng\'e0y th\'e0nh l\u7853 p tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a ch\'fang ch\'e1u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Chung Vi\uc0\u7877 n th\u7871  m\'e0 \u7903  th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y tr\'ed nh\u7899  l\u7841 i v\'f4 c\'f9ng t\u7889 t: "K\u7927  ni\u7879 m ng\'e0y th\'e0nh l\u7853 p tr\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i v\'e0o th\'e1ng t\u432  \u432 ? H\'e0ng n\u259 m \u273 \u7873 u ngh\u7881  li\u7873 n v\u7899 i ng\'e0y 1/5 m\'e0? Sao l\u7841 i ngh\u7881  v\'e0o l\'fac n\'e0y?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915  \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c \u273 \u7871 n nghi\'ean c\u7913 u sinh \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7893 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7889 n n\u259 m tr\'f4i qua d\'f9 sao \'f4ng c\u361 ng c\'f3 ch\'fat \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'f2ng t\uc0\u7921  nh\u7911  xong r\u7891 i, l\u7897  r\u7891 i. Nh\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i \u273 i\u7873 m t\u297 nh \u273 \'e1p n\'f3i: "Th\u7901 i kh\'e1ng chi\u7871 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng d\u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n T\'e2y Nam m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian sao \u7841 ? \u272 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac kh\'e1ng chi\u7871 n th\u7855 ng l\u7907 i m\u7899 i chuy\u7875 n v\u7873  l\u7841 i. K\u7927  ni\u7879 m ng\'e0y th\'e0nh l\u7853 p tr\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7847 n n\'e0y ch\'ednh l\'e0 ch\'fac m\u7915 ng kh\'e1ng chi\u7871 n th\u7855 ng l\u7907 i kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c tr\u432 \u417 \u768 ng, nh\u7919 ng n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881 , n\u259 m nay l\'e0 b\u7843 y m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m kh\'e1ng chi\u7871 n th\u7855 ng l\u7907 i cho n\'ean \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t ch\'fac m\u7915 ng \u7841 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngay c\uc0\u7843  Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng nghe \u273 \u7871 n s\u7919 ng s\u7919 ng s\u7901  s\u7901 , Tr\'ec Chung Vi\u7877 n l\u7841 i c\'e0ng tin, li\'ean t\u7909 c g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "Th\'ec ra l\'e0 th\u7871 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t b\u7897  d\u7841 ng suy s\u7909 p, n\'f3i trong nh\'e0 "C\'f3 y\'eau t\'e0 mu\u7889 n l\'e0m h\u7841 i", Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873 . Nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i n\u7897 i t\'ecnh th\u7843 m \'e1n li\'ean ti\u7871 p \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A v\'e0 chuy\u7879 n C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch v\u7899 i cha m\u7865 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng ph\u7889 i h\u7907 p di\u7877 n k\u7883 ch v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, l\'fac cha m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7887 i ch\u7881  n\'f3i l\'e0 m\'ecnh v\u7851 n lu\'f4n nghe n\'f3i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  H phong c\u7843 nh \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, thu \u273 \'f4ng \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 v\u7867  \u273 \u7865 p kh\'e1c nhau, cho n\'ean m\u7899 i nh\'e2n d\u7883 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881  c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873  tham quan.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7873  nh\'e0 khi \u273 \'e3 mu\u7897 n, n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n m\u7897 t l\'e1t th\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7899 m, \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n th\u7901 i gian \u273 i ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 nh\'e0 \uc0\u7903  ph\u7893  th\'f4ng, di\u7879 n t\'edch tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7887  nh\u432 ng ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m, m\u7897 t nam m\u7897 t b\u7855 c hai ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng s\'e1ch, m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng h\u417 i nh\u7887  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'f9ng nh\u432  ph\'f2ng tr\u7919  \u273 \u7891 , c\'f2n d\u432  l\u7841 i ch\'ednh l\'e0 ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, ph\'f2ng \u259 n, ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p, ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m c\'e1c lo\u7841 i, b\u7903 i v\'ec b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i ng\u7911  l\u7841 i cho n\'ean c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7845 t thi\u7871 t s\u7855 p x\u7871 p "Ph\'f2ng cho kh\'e1ch", ph\'f2ng c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7911  ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai c\u259 n. C\u361 ng may ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'e1 l\u7899 n, c\'f2n d\'f9ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u m\u7863 c \u273 \u7883 nh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean n\'ean ng\u7911  c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 m\uc0\u7897 t nh\'e0 v\u7879  sinh nh\u7887 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi sau khi t\u7915  trong \u273 \'f3 \u273 i ra li\u7873 n th\'edch \'fd chi\u7871 m n\u7917 a gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 b\u7889 n ph\'eda, h\u7887 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "A Di\'ean, t\u7915  nh\u7887  c\u7853 u ng\u7911  \u7903  \u273 \'e2y \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 t\u7915  nh\u7887 , \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i l\'fac l\'ean c\u7845 p hai th\'ec chuy\u7875 n t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean v\u432 \u417 n tay t\u7899 i \'f4m m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u7853 u m\u7899 i \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c, m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7873  C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7915  r\u7845 t l\'e2u r\u7891 i, th\u7871  n\'ean c\'f3 l\u7869  ngay t\u7915  l\'fac b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh l\'e0 phu qu\'e2n "Di\u7879 p tam khi\u7871 m" trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, b\u7903 i v\'ec C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch cho n\'ean l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c gi\u7843  b\u7897  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh m\'e0 th\'f4i. B\'e2y gi\u7901  n\'f3i ra r\u7891 i, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\u7897  r\'f5 b\u7843 n t\'ednh?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m c\u7853 u k\u7873  c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895  n\u7857 m d\u7921 a v\'e0o \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7855 n tai c\u7853 u kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u v\'f4 l\u432 \u417 ng t\'e2m nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7913 ? T\'f4i l\'e1i xe n\u259 m ti\u7871 ng c\'f9ng c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7863 p cha m\u7865 , c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u432 \u7903 ng g\'ec cho t\'f4i \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Mu\uc0\u7889 n, mu\u7889 n th\u432 \u7903 ng c\'e1i g\'ec..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i, \u273 \u7871 n khi ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p li\u7873 n v\u7897 i v\'e0ng b\u7893  sung, "... Gi\u7901  \u273 ang \u7903  nh\'e0 t\'f4i, c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng l\'e0m b\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7881  h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i, h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i..." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i xong, thanh \'e2m d\u7847 n d\u7847 n t\u7889 i xu\u7889 ng...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7889  \'fd mang Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7873  ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \u7875  ph\'f2ng b\u7883  C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  cha m\u7865  c\'e1ch xa, cho c\'f4 ta th\u7901 i c\u417  l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng. V\'ec v\u7853 y n\u7917 a c\u7913 ng r\u7855 n n\u7917 a l\'e0m n\u361 ng s\u7855 p x\u7871 p m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n du l\u7883 ch \u7903  khu danh lam th\u7855 ng c\u7843 nh \u7903  v\'f9ng ph\u7909  c\u7853 n ba ng\'e0y, k\'eau cha m\u7865  xin ngh\u7881  \u273 i c\'f9ng, t\'ednh t\'ednh to\'e1n to\'e1n th\u7901 i gian, ch\u7901  m\u7897 t hai ng\'e0y sau tr\u7903  v\u7873  th\'ec H\u7891  Tinh h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 quay l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7899 m bi\u7871 t cha m\u7865  \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p v\u7873  h\u432 u, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f4ng t\'e1c c\u361 ng thong th\u7843 , trong ba ng\'e0y c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y l\'e0 Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t, b\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7843  nh\'e0 c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i du l\u7883 ch, xin ngh\u7881  hai ng\'e0y kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Qu\u7843  nhi\'ean hai v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng th\u7845 y con trai \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p x\u7871 p xong xu\'f4i h\u7871 t th\u7843 y c\u361 ng vui v\u7867  chu\u7849 n b\u7883  c\'f9ng \u273 i, nhi\u7873 u nh\u7845 t l\'e0 n\'f3i ngo\'e0i mi\u7879 ng hai c\'e2u "Hai thanh ni\'ean \u273 i ch\u417 i ch\'fang ta \u273 i theo l\'e0m g\'ec", nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n vui s\u432 \u7899 ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c c\u7847 n mang \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  tu\u7893 i c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng l\u7899 n, hai n\u259 m qua th\u7901 i gian \u7903  c\'f9ng con trai c\u361 ng c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng \'edt, c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i ch\u417 i nh\u432  th\u7871  th\u7853 t ra trong l\'f2ng r\u7845 t vui.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7845 y c\u7899  ngh\u7881  tr\u432 a k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o ph\'f2ng, tr\u7903  tay kh\'f3a c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, k\'e9o c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m l\'ean ch\'f3p m\u361 i c\u7853 u: "C\u7853 u nha, nh\'ecn qua ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chi\u7873 u quen, trong nh\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng theo \'fd c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 a tay tr\u7889 n ng\'f3n tay c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u417  h\u7897 i, \u273 \'e8 l\u7841 i h\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u417 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t khu sinh th\'e1i nguy\'ean sinh, thi\'ean nhi\'ean ch\u432 a b\u7883  \'f4 nhi\u7877 m ch\'fat n\'e0o, c\'f3 m\u7897 t h\u7891  n\u432 \u7899 c h\'ecnh tr\u259 ng l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7873 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\'f3ng b\u432 \u7899 c nh\'ecn c\u7843 nh h\u7891 , h\'edp m\u7855 t c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "H\'ecnh nh\u432  t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng t\u7899 i n\u417 i n\'e0y r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ph\'eda sau c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n l\'ean tai c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843  kinh, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng tr\u7897 m li\u7871 c cha m\u7865  \u273 ang ng\u7855 m c\u7843 nh b\'ean kia, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i nh\u7845 c m\u7855 t kh\u7869  tr\u7915 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, y\u7871 u \u7899 t kh\'e1ng ngh\u7883 : "C\u7853 u ch\'fa \'fd m\u7897 t ch\'fat..." N\'f3i xong t\u7921  b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\u7901 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ch\'fat s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh, thay v\'ec n\'f3i l\'e0 kh\'e1ng ngh\u7883  ch\u7859 ng b\u7857 ng n\'f3i l\'e0 l\'e0m n\u361 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  l\'e0 l\u7841 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i\u7879 u m\u7897 t l\u7847 n: "... \'cdt nh\u7845 t ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n t\u7889 i v\u7873 ." 
