\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f3 m\'e0 \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng s\u7869  d\'f9ng c\'e1ch th\u7913 c g\'ec xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi theo s\'e1t sau l\u432 ng cha m\u7865  m\u7897 t gi\'e2y kh\'f4ng r\u7901 i, l\'fac t\'ecm n\u417 i ngh\u7881  l\u7841 i c\u361 ng ch\u7885 n ch\u7895  c\'f3 hai ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y \uc0\u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng Tr\'ec Chung Vi\u7877 n v\u7851 n c\'f2n xua Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Hai thanh ni\'ean tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 i ch\u417 i \u273 i, \u273 \u7915 ng b\'e1m theo hai ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0 n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\uc0\u7873 n ti\u7871 n t\u7899 i \'f4m c\'e1nh tay L\u432 u Ph\u432 \u7907 ng O\'e1nh l\'e0m n\u361 ng c\u432 \u7901 i: "Me\u803 , con trai mu\u7889 n b\u7891 i m\u7865  v\'e0 cha m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u432 u Ph\u432 \u7907 ng O\'e1nh x\u7845 u h\u7893  quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i l\'e9n nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i con trai: "Sao l\u7899 n th\u7871  n\'e0y r\u7891 i m\'e0 v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ho\'e0ng nghi\'eam ch\u7881 nh, \u273 \u7873 u t\u7841 i cha m\u7865  l\'e0m h\u432  con r\u7891 i, m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nam t\u7917  h\'e1n, \u273 \u7875  b\u7841 n h\u7885 c ch\'ea c\u432 \u7901 i." Trong mi\u7879 ng l\u7849 m b\u7849 m, ng\u7919  kh\'ed nh\u432 ng l\'e0 b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  l\u7841 i dung t\'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i theo ph\'eda sau nh\'ecn c\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 i, c\u361 ng tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i cha m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7901 i gian ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t ng\'e0y v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng Tr\'ec Chung Vi\u7877 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng th\'e2n thi\u7871 t, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9 n\'e0y t\'ednh c\'e1ch \u273 i\u7873 m \u273 \u7841 m, tr\u7847 m \u7893 n \u273 \'e1ng tin c\u7853 y, kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng con trai nh\'e0 m\'ecnh c\u7843  ng\'e0y gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u432 a l\u7899 n, l\'e0m b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng an t\'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i l\'fac ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m eo Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ch\'f4n \u7903  c\u7847 n c\u7893  c\u7853 u n\u7881  non n\'f3i: "Ch\u7915 ng n\'e0o th\'ec c\u7853 u m\u7899 i n\'f3i c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n b\u7891 i \'f4ng x\'e3, t\'f4i \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh th\u7845 y m\'e0 ph\'e1t ghen."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7849 y h\u7855 n, b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng h\'f4n l\'ean m\u7855 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec c\u7913  v\u7909 ng tr\u7897 m ch\u417 i \u273 \'f9a \u273 \u7871 n ng\'e1n ba ng\'e0y nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\u7899 i l\'e1i xe b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u quay v\u7873 , m\u7885 i th\u7913  ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\'ecnh an v\'f4 s\u7921 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u t\u7899 i cu\u7889 i lu\'f4n l\u432 u t\'e2m \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng, nh\u432 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\'e2n \u7843 nh h\u432  h\u432  th\u7921 c th\u7921 c c\u7911 a C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi tr\uc0\u7903  v\u7873  th\'ec \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 ng\'e0y th\u7913  n\u259 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  H, Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\'ednh to\'e1n kho\u7843 ng hai ng\'e0y n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 tin t\u7913 c c\u7911 a H\u7891  Tinh, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n H\u7891  Tinh kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u d\'f5i theo C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, m\'ecnh v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 th\u7875  y\'ean t\'e2m r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  nh\'e0 li\'ean t\u7909 c ba ng\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  L\u432 u Ph\u432 \u7907 ng O\'e1nh mu\u7889 n k\'e9o ch\u7891 ng \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i mua th\u7913 c \u259 n, b\u7883  Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u259 n c\u7843 n: "M\u7865 , m\u7865  v\u7899 i cha \u7903  nh\'e0 d\u7885 n d\u7865 p nh\'e0 c\u7917 a, xem tivi, tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Ngh\'eanh Chi, mu\u7889 n mua g\'ec th\'ec vi\u7871 t ra gi\u7845 y cho con, con \u273 i mua l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  l\'e0 ban ng\'e0y, trong l\'f2ng m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u r\'f5 chuy\u7879 n, \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i m\u7897 t l\'e1t c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec x\u7843 y ra, m\u7845 u ch\u7889 t l\'e0 ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i v\u7899 i cha m\u7865 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u432 u Ph\u432 \u7907 ng O\'e1nh ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y con trai l\u7847 n n\'e0y tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c kia, nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  cho l\'e0 c\u7853 u c\'e0ng l\u7899 n c\'e0ng hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t, li\u7879 t k\'ea ra gi\u7845 y m\u7897 t lo\u7841 t l\u7841 i d\u7863 n d\'f2 m\u7897 t h\u7891 i r\u7891 i \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i mua th\u7913 c \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c khi \u273 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i l\u7863 ng l\u7869  d\u7863 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\'f4i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i m\u7897 t l\'e1t. N\u7871 u nh\u432 , t\'f4i n\'f3i l\'e0 n\u7871 u nh\u432  C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch ho\u7863 c ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7889 ng C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i ng\u259 n ba m\u7865  t\'f4i kh\'f4ng cho m\u7903  c\u7917 a, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  c\'f4 ta ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n ba m\u7865  t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "T\'f4i bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i. C\u7853 u l\'e0 l\'e0m vi\u7879 c tr\'e1i v\u7899 i l\u432 \u417 ng t\'e2m n\'ean m\u7899 i t\u7915  xa ho\u7843 ng s\u7907  v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ch\u7841 y v\u7873  tr\u7889 n C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f2n kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh th\'e2n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i hay sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'f2ng th\uc0\u7847 m o\'e1n, nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua b\'ean trong c\u7917 a, cha m\u7865  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 ang \u7903  trong b\u7871 p, kh\'f4ng \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch. B\'e8n nhanh ch\'f3ng ki\u7877 ng ch\'e2n h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i l\'ean m\u7863 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "V\u7853 y nh\u7901  c\u7853 u, t\'f4i \u273 i \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7913 t l\u7901 i ch\u7841 y th\u7853 t nhanh ra ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  huy\u7873 n quan, tay tr\'e1i v\u7851 n \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean c\u7917 a, nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhanh ch\'f3ng r\u7901 i \u273 i, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac c\u7853 u \u273 i th\u7853 t l\'e2u ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a m\u7899 i kh\u7869  \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, cong \'e1nh m\u7855 t im \u7855 ng c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ti\uc0\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i..."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 ang x\'e1ch \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 i v\u7873  nh\'e0 th\'ec nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\u7865  m\'ecnh, L\u432 u Ph\u432 \u7907 ng O\'e1nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u432 u Ph\u432 \u7907 ng O\'e1nh gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang tr\u7889 n \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 l\'e9n l\'fat g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, c\u7889  \'fd nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean nha, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\'f4 g\'e1i c\u7921 c k\'ec xinh \u273 \u7865 p t\'ecm \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ch\'fang ta, m\u7865  nh\'ecn qua M\u7855 t m\'e8o r\u7891 i. Con b\'e9 n\'f3i n\'f3 l\'e0 b\u7841 n g\'e1i con, m\u7865  \u273 ang th\u7847 m ngh\u297  con c\'f3 b\u7841 n g\'e1i khi n\'e0o th\'ec Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 \u273 i t\u7899 i, t\u7921  m\u7903  c\u7917 a \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 ang n\'f3i g\'ec v\u7899 i con b\'e9. M\u7865  qu\u7843  th\u7921 c kh\'f4ng r\'f5 t\'ecnh h\'ecnh nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o cho n\'ean mu\u7889 n g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7887 i con tr\u432 \u7899 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe xong li\uc0\u7873 n n\'f3ng n\u7843 y:\
"Ngh\'eanh Chi m\uc0\u7903  c\u7917 a r\u7891 i \u7841 ? \u272 i ra ngo\'e0i r\u7891 i? B\'e2y gi\u7901  v\u7851 n ch\u432 a tr\u7903  l\u7841 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7903  c\u7917 a sao? C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch ra tay v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i g\uc0\u7885 i l\'e0 hi\u7875 u con kh\'f4ng ai b\u7857 ng m\u7865 , L\u432 u Ph\u432 \u7907 ng O\'e1nh l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nghe ra c\u7845 p b\'e1ch v\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a con trai, tuy c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f3 hi\u7875 u nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n an \u7911 i: "Con \u273 \u7915 ng g\u7845 p, \u273 \u7875  m\u7865  \u273 i xem th\u7917 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t b\'ean c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\u7897 t b\'ean v\u7897 i v\'e3 tr\u7903  v\u7873 , ch\u7881  l\'e1t sau \u273 \'e3 nghe th\u7845 y m\u7865  m\'ecnh \u7903  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'ean kia n\'f3i: "V\u7873  r\u7891 i, t\u7921  Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7873 , kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y n\u7919  sinh kia \u273 \'e2u c\u7843 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7899 i d\'e3n ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, m\u7865  \'e0, n\u7919  sinh kia kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7841 n g\'e1i c\u7911 a con, th\u7847 n kinh c\'f4 ta c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t... V\'e2ng, c\'f2n l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  v\u7873  n\'f3i ti\u7871 p, con c\'fap m\'e1y \u273 \'e3."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i v\uc0\u7899 i m\u7865  m\'ecnh l\'e0 th\u7847 n kinh C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , chung quy so v\u7899 i n\'f3i cho b\'e0 bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  d\u7877  ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi v\uc0\u7873  nh\'e0 \u273 i v\'e0o b\u7871 p bu\'f4ng \u273 \u7891  xu\u7889 ng li\u7873 n b\u7893  nh\'e0o v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang xem s\'e1ch trong ph\'f2ng s\'e1ch, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng qu\'ean tr\u7903  tay \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7875  s\'e1ch trong tay xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, v\u7915 a v\u7863 n ti\u7871 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, \u273 \u7905  hai c\'e1nh tay c\u7853 u h\u7887 i: "A Di\'ean, l\'e0m sao th\u7871 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nu\uc0\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng, cao th\u7845 p \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 h\u7855 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, l\u7841 i th\'f2 tay s\u7901  s\u7901  th\'e2n th\u7875  h\u7855 n, x\'e1c nh\u7853 n h\u7855 n v\u7851 n l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'ecnh bi\u7871 t, v\u7851 n ho\'e0n h\u7843 o kh\'f4ng t\u7893 n hao g\'ec m\u7899 i ch\'ednh th\u7913 c th\u7903  ph\'e0o: "C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4n h\'f4n tr\'e1n c\u7853 u: "C\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec. L\'fac b\'e1c g\'e1i \u273 ang mu\u7889 n m\u7903  c\u7917 a cho c\'f4 ta, t\'f4i nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng n\'ean \u273 i qua, c\'f4 ta v\u7915 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y t\'f4i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'e3 \u273 i m\u7845 t. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\u7853 u v\u7899 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch l\'e0 th\u7871  n\'e0o? Sao c\'f4 ta c\'f2n bi\u7871 t nh\'e0 c\u7853 u? C\'f2n \u273 u\u7893 i theo \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n \u273 \'e2y r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng x\'e1c nh\u7853 n quan h\u7879 , nh\u432 ng trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 t\u7921  th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nghi ng\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n khi\u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi hi\u7875 u l\u7847 m, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c gi\u7845 u ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a m\'ecnh n\u7919 a, v\'ec v\u7853 y ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn h\u7855 n nghi\'eam t\'fac n\'f3i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i n\'f3i c\'f3 y\'eau t\'e0 mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 t\'f4i, ch\'ednh l\'e0 n\'f3i c\'f4 ta. C\'f4 ta c\u361 ng l\'e0 hung th\u7911  c\u7911 a \'e1n m\u7841 ng li\'ean ho\'e0n tr\u432 \u7899 c kia. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec sao, c\'f4 ta c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh gi\u7843 i th\'edch qu\'e1 k\u7929 , nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i n\'e0y, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tham d\u7921  qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u, bi\u7871 t C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd t\u7889 t, sau n\'e0y tr\'e1nh c\'f4 ta \u273 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng v\'f4 l\u7921 c, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n l\'e0m h\u7871 t s\u7913 c \u273 \u7875  b\u7843 o v\u7879  ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  h\u7855 n ti\u7871 p x\'fac nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Cho n\'ean nh\uc0\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n h\u7887 i, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n sau n\'e0y c\'e1ch xa c\'f4 ta m\u7897 t ch\'fat, tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n, c\u7853 u c\u7913  tr\'e1nh xa c\'f4 ta ra."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c," \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t tin t\u7913 c kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng nh\u432  th\u7871 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  t\u7887  v\u7867  ho\'e0i nghi m\'e0 nh\'ecn c\u7853 u nghi\'eam t\'fac \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, "T\u7845 t c\u7843  t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u nghe c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i gi\'fap cha m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7845 u c\u417 m, b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i trong nh\'e0 vui v\u7867  \u7845 m \'e1p, th\u7853 t gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\u7845 t an, lo l\u7855 ng C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch ch\u432 a t\u7915  b\u7887  \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  ch\u7901  th\u7901 i c\u417  quay l\u7841 i, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i sau khi c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a, m\u7897 t m\u7921 c nghe \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh b\'ean ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi du\u7895 i c\'e1nh tay qua \'f4m c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "Ng\u7911  \u273 i, ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\'f3 t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y r\u7891 i. T\'f4i v\'e0 c\u7853 u c\'f9ng ch\'fa \'fd.", c\u7853 u m\u7899 i nghe l\u7901 i tho\'e1ng m\u417  m\'e0ng ng\u7911  m\u7897 t l\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam v\'f4 s\u7921 , h\'f4m sau bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a l\'fac \u259 n c\u417 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin t\u7889 t, A S\'eanh \u273 \'e3 tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i nguy hi\u7875 m, H\u7891  Tinh hi\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 v\u7873  t\u7899 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A, h\u417 n n\u7919 a t\u7853 p trung v\'e0o C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe xong vui m\u7915 ng nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng \'e2m th\u7847 m kinh h\'e3i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \'e3 d\'f9ng bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p g\'ec, nhanh nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 i theo b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i n\'e0y, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i trong v\'f2ng m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam v\u7873  t\u7899 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7891 n ch\u7891 n, d\u7921 a theo l\u7901 i H\u7891  Tinh n\'f3i, k\'fd th\u7875  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i 'C\'f4 ta' h\u7859 n l\'e0 c\u7921 c k\'ec quan tr\u7885 ng, li\'ean quan t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n s\u7889 ng ch\u7871 t, 'C\'f4 ta' s\u7869  d\u7877  d\'e0ng bu\'f4ng tha nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y c\u7853 u v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n c\u7889  \'fd \u7903  l\u7841 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  H \u7903  b\'ean cha m\u7865  n\u7919 a, l\u7845 y c\u7899  n\'f3i ph\u7843 i \u273 i h\u7885 c xong li\u7873 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c chu\u7849 n b\u7883  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7907  ch\u7891 ng Tr\'ec Chung Vi\u7877 n v\u7851 n r\u7845 t l\u432 u luy\u7871 n kh\'f4ng r\u7901 i, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  cho hai ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t \u273 \u7889 ng \u273 \u7891  \u259 n mang \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m tr\u7903  l\u7841 i nh\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 h\u417 n ch\'edn gi\u7901  t\u7889 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean mang \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c s\u7855 p x\u7871 p v\u7873  v\u7883  tr\'ed c\u361  xong li\u7873 n c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m t\u7855 m \'97\'97 tuy r\u7857 ng trong nh\'e0 c\'f2n c\'f3 ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m kh\'e1c, nh\u432 ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7881  th\u432 \u7901 ng d\'f9ng ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m trong ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7891 i tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7855 m r\u7917 a xong \u273 i ra \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u c\u432 \u7901 i h\u7887 i: "A Di\'ean, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i nghe l\u7901 i c\u7853 u \u273 u\u7893 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 i r\u7891 i, c\'f3 ph\u7847 n th\u432 \u7903 ng g\'ec kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u432 \u7903 ng?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u432 a k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\'f3 ch\'fat m\u7901  m\u7883 t n\'f3i. "C\u7853 u mu\u7889 n th\u432 \u7903 ng g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ng\u7891 i tr\'ean m\'e9p gi\u432 \u7901 ng, th\'e2n th\u7875  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n m\u7903  ra, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u ng\u432 \u7899 c nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, b\u7897  d\'e1ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n t\'edn nhi\u7879 m, trong m\u7855 t c\'f2n mang theo h\u417 i n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn v\'e0o trong m\u7855 t, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \u7849 y c\u7853 u ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, th\u7847 m th\'ec n\'f3i: "Th\u432 \u7903 ng g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c? L\'e0 c\u7853 u n\'f3i \u273 \'f3?" \'c2m cu\u7889 i h\u417 i cao l\'ean, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng sung s\u432 \u7899 ng m\'e0 th\u7887 a m\'e3n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac n\'e0y m\uc0\u7899 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'fd c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, m\u7863 t tho\u7855 t c\'e1i \u273 \u7887  l\'ean, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n v\'f9i v\'e0o vai h\u7855 n, \'e2m thanh c\u7921 c nh\u7887  "\u7914 " m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, c\u7843 m th\u7909  \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7851 n c\u7843 m c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'fac \'e1o s\u417 mi r\u7897 ng th\'f9ng th\'ecnh b\u7843 n th\'e2n t\'f9y ti\u7879 n m\u7863 c l\'ean sau khi t\u7855 m xong b\u7883  h\u7855 n t\u7915 ng n\'fat c\u7903 i b\u7887 , ng\'f3n tay h\u417 i l\u7841 nh g\u7841 t v\u7841 t \'e1o sang hai b\'ean, s\u7901  l\'ean ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u...\cb1 \
\cb3 To\'e0n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng k\'ecm \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c run l\'ean, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u7883 n xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u7903  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang d\'e1n ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y m\'ecnh, y\'ean t\'e2m \'f4m l\u7845 y h\u7855 n, m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y, l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'f3. Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec kh\'e1c, kh\'f4ng n\'ean ngh\u297  lung tung...\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 em c\u7853 u to\'e0n b\u7897  nh\'e9t v\'e0o trong ph\u7841 m vi kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7895  l\u7921 c kh\u7855 c ch\u7871 , nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c run l\'ean.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t kh\u7889 i d\u7915 ng \u7903  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u kia, sau \u273 \'f3 h\'f4n nh\u7865 , h\u417 i th\u7903  mang theo c\u7843 m gi\'e1c h\u417 i l\u7841 nh kia, b\'e0n tay \'f4m b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng tr\'eau \u273 \'f9a kia, m\u7895 i th\u7913 ,... \u273 \u7873 u qu\'e1 gi\u7889 ng, t\u7921 a nh\u432  trong ch\u7899 p m\u7855 t k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\u7873  t\u7899 i \u273 \'eam h\'e8 n\u259 m \u273 \'f3, Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng nh\u7887  h\u7865 p ng\u7897 t ng\u7841 t m\'e0 h\u7855 c \'e1m, *quang \u7843 nh m\'e0u cam chi\u7871 u loang l\u7893  tr\'ean t\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'f9ng v\u7899 i t\u432 \u7907 ng Ph\u7853 t t\u7893  B\u7891  T\'e1t t\u7915  bi ...\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (quang \uc0\u7843 nh: chi\u7871 u qua c\u7917 a s\u7893  in l\'ean t\u432 \u7901 ng)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  k\'edch th\'edch n\u7913 c n\u7903  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7849 y ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean th\'e2n ra, co l\u7841 i tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng lui v\u7873  ph\'eda \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng, run m\'f4i nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\u7921 a h\u7891  mu\u7889 n th\u7845 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng, xuy\'ean qua l\u7899 p da n\'e0y nh\'ecn th\u7845 u h\u7855 n: "... C\u7853 u l\'e0 ai? C\u7853 u r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 ai?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  bi\u7871 n c\u7889  b\u7845 t ng\u7901  kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng n\'e0y d\u7885 a s\u7907 , ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, trong con ng\u432 \u417 i m\'e0u \u273 en c\'f3 kh\'f3 hi\u7875 u, v\'f4 t\u7897 i, v\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\u7895  l\u7921 c b\'ecnh ph\u7909 c t\'ecnh tri\u7873 u v\'e0 h\'f4 h\u7845 p, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng v\u432 \u417 n tay v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 n\'f3i: "L\'e0 t\'f4i, A Di\'ean, l\'e0 t\'f4i \u273 \'e2y, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, n\u432 \u417 ng t\u7917  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, \'f4ng x\'e3 c\u7853 u... C\u7853 u l\'e0m sao th\u7871 ? L\u7841 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean lui \uc0\u7903  \u273 \'f3 nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i l\u7897  ra ch\'fat th\'e2n th\u7875 , v\u432 \u417 n tay ph\u7843 i \u273 \'e1p tr\'ean tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4n h\'f2a, mang theo ch\'fat c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'e1t, kh\u7899 p x\u432 \u417 ng thon d\'e0i m\'e0 r\'f5 r\'e0ng, l\'e0 tay c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng sai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7875  ch\u7845 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi thi\'ean l\u7841 nh, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bao nhi\'eau l\uc0\u7847 n s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c kinh ho\u7843 ng b\u7845 t l\u7921 c, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 \u273 \'f4i tay n\'e0y \'f4m c\u7853 u, v\u7895  v\u7873  vai c\u7853 u vu\u7889 t s\u7889 ng l\u432 ng c\u7853 u an \u7911 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi... ?" C\u7853 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng x\'e1c nh\u7853 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  con th\'fa nh\u7887  b\u7883  kinh h\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7843 o b\u7889 i, l\'e0 t\'f4i \u273 \'e2y." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, trong \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7917  m\'e0u \u273 en chi\u7871 u ra th\'e2n \u7843 nh c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng chuy\uc0\u7875 n con ng\u432 \u417 i nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng t\u7915 ng ch\'fat m\u7897 t n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t tay h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t l\u7853 p t\u7913 c d\'f9ng s\u7913 c k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, v\u7919 ng v\'e0ng \'f4m ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng sao, nghe l\u7901 i, \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907 , t\'f4i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u432 \u417 ng t\u7893 n c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'ed t\uc0\u7913 c v\'e0 \'f4m \u226 \u769 p quen thu\u7897 c, \u273 \'e2y th\u7853 t l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng sai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  \u273 \u7849 y h\u7855 n: "... Ngh\'eanh Chi, xin l\u7895 i. H\'f4m nay t\'f4i mu\u7889 n sang ph\'f2ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh ng\u7911 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi bu\'f4ng c\u7853 u ra, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u s\u7901  l\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7853 u: "Kh\'f4ng sao, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n x\u7845 u h\u7893 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, \u7845 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean nguy\'ean t\u7841 i ch\u7895 : "C\u7853 u ngh\u7881  \u7903  \u273 \'e2y \u273 i, t\'f4i sang ph\'f2ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n l\u7841 i kh\u7869  h\'f4n \u273 \u7881 nh \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Ch\u7915 ng n\'e0o c\u7853 u g\u7885 i t\'f4i tr\u7903  l\u7841 i th\'ec t\'f4i s\u7869  tr\u7903  l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\uc0\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m ch\u259 n g\u7889 i \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t ch\u259 n, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c lu\u7889 ng cu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\'e0ng \'f4n nhu khoan dung, c\'e0ng bao dung r\u7897 ng l\u432 \u7907 ng, c\u7853 u l\u7841 i c\'e0ng \'e1y n\'e1y, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ngh\u297  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 m\'ecnh tr\'e1ch oan Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7891 i, Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0 'N\u432 \u417 ng t\u7917 ' c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ch\u417 i tr\'f2 ch\u417 i hai n\u259 m, b\u7903 i v\'ec l\'e0 \u273 \u7891 ng t\'ednh n\'ean ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p kh\'f4ng d\'e1m g\u7863 p m\u7863 t c\u7853 u; l\'e0 b\u7841 n c\'f9ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u; c\u361 ng l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u432 \u417 ng v\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 li\'ean h\u7879  v\u7899 i th\u7913  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m g\'ec, tr\u432 \u7899 c khi \u7903  b\'ean Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  t\u7915 ng c\'f3 ti\u7871 p x\'fac th\'e2n m\u7853 t v\u7899 i th\u7913  kia, th\u7853 m ch\'ed ngay c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  m\'e0 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u nam sinh th\u7901 i k\'ec d\u7853 y th\'ec b\u7903 i v\'ec t\'f2 m\'f2 s\u7869  xem c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t \'edt xem. C\'f3 l\u7869  do qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh v\'e0 \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c nhau l\u7855 m, c\u361 ng c\'f3 l\u7869  b\u7903 i l\u7847 n \u7903  Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng kia, tr\'ed nh\u7899  v\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c d\u432 \u7899 i \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7911 a n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i \u273 \'e3 kh\u7855 c qu\'e1 s\'e2u \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i sinh ra nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c sai...\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\u7851 n c\'f2n ho\'e0i nghi c\'e1i g\'ec, ho\'e0i nghi h\u7855 n b\u7883  th\u7913  kia nh\u7853 p hay sao...\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi b\uc0\u7883  \'fd ni\u7879 m n\'e0y trong \u273 \u7847 u d\u7885 a c\u7843  kinh, c\u7853 u l\u7841 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u ph\u7911  nh\u7853 n, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i \'e1nh m\u7855 t kia c\u7911 a Ngh\'eanh Chi, l\'e0 kh\'f4ng l\'e0m gi\u7843  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \'f3, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn c\u7853 u r\u7845 t l\'e2u, t\'ecm c\u7853 u r\u7845 t l\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi\uc0\u7871 n cho c\u7853 u m\u7895 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 c\uc0\u7853 u qu\'e1 nghi th\u7847 n nghi qu\u7927  r\u7891 i, m\u7845 y ng\'e0y nay b\u7883  C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u th\u7847 n kinh l\u7841 i c\'e0ng c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ch\u7853 m r\'e3i d\'f9ng ch\u259 n qu\u7845 n m\'ecnh l\u7841 i, m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng ngh\u297 , ng\'e0y mai, ng\'e0y mai s\u7869  g\u7885 i Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'ednh m\'ecnh l\uc0\u7841 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, b\u7891 i th\u432 \u7901 ng cho h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t c\u7853 u h\u417 i n\'f3ng l\'ean, c\u7913  ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432  v\u7853 y ti\u7871 n v\'e0o m\u7897 ng \u273 \u7865 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ch\'ecm v\'e0o m\u7897 ng c\u7843 nh, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  bi\u7871 t r\u7857 ng sau khi c\u7853 u ng\u7911  say c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  li\u7873 n b\u7883  m\u7903  ra, m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7863 ng l\u7869  ti\u7871 n v\'e0o, kh\u7869  k\'e9o m\u7873 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u n\u7857 m v\'e0o, t\u7915  sau l\u432 ng bao l\u7845 y c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7889  \'fd ch\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7853 y t\u7915  tr\'ean xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i nh\'ecn b\u7897  d\'e1ng c\u7853 u ng\u7911 , qua h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng k\'e9o ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, ch\u7841 m nh\u7865  l\'ean m\u361 i c\u7853 u: "Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i, c\'f2n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 v\'ec c\u7853 u \u432 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec c\uc0\u7853 u, m\u7845 t h\u7891 n, t\'e1n ph\'e1ch, ngay c\u7843  t\'e2m c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  m\'ea.\cb1 \
