\cb3 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, th\u7845 y b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng quen.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi r\uc0\u7901 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u c\u7889  \'fd sang ph\'f2ng b\'eanh c\u7841 nh xem th\u7917 , ch\u7881  th\u7845 y gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\u7911  g\u7885 n g\'e0ng, h\u7847 u nh\u432  nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng ra d\u7845 u v\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7911 ; c\u7853 u l\u7841 i \u273 i xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\u7843  nhi\'ean \u273 \'e3 d\u7853 y, \u273 ang \u7903  trong b\u7871 p l\'e0m b\u7919 a s\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\u432 ng cao ng\u7845 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, t\'ecnh \'fd v\'e0 \'e1y n\'e1y t\u7915 ng tr\u7853 n c\'f9ng nhau x\'f4ng l\'ean \u273 \u7847 u, c\u7853 u chu\u7849 n b\u7883  m\u7897 t l\'e1t r\u7891 i m\u7899 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "Ngh\'eanh Chi."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\u361 ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u273 \'f3 t\u7855 t l\u7917 a, \u273 em m\'ec \'dd x\'e0o rau v\'e0 ti\'eau \u273 en chia v\'e0o hai \u273 \u297 a s\u7913  m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng r\u7891 i b\u432 ng ra, l\u7841 i c\u7847 m hai c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c chanh trong l\'e0nh t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7895 i bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0u s\uc0\u7855 c h\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7911  l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng m\u7845 t dinh d\u432 \u7905 ng, m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n b\u7843 y ng\'e0y b\u7919 a s\'e1ng b\u7919 a tr\u432 a, mi\u7877 n l\'e0 \u259 n \u7903  nh\'e0 th\'ec s\u7869  kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nhau. Ch\u7881  t\u7915  c\u417 m canh \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\'ec cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng sinh ho\u7841 t c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 hao t\u7893 n bao nhi\'eau t\'e2m t\u432 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, nghe \u273 \u7891  \u259 n m\'f9i th\u417 m, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'e0ng th\'eam \'e1y n\'e1y: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, xin l\u7895 i, b\u7903 i g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y qu\'e1 kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng cho n\'ean h\'f4m qua t\'f4i m\u7899 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y. H\'f4m nay c\u7853 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ng\u7911  \u273 i, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 a tay s\u7901  s\u7901  m\u7863 t c\u7853 u: "C\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'e1 h\u417 n ch\'fat n\'e0o ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m n\u432 \u7899 c chanh xong m\u7899 i quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7853 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 i. Ch\'ednh l\'e0... mu\u7889 n th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c..."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong l\uc0\u7901 i n\'e0y c\u7853 u li\u7873 n tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn v\'e0o m\u7855 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, \'e2m cu\u7889 i c\u361 ng c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng th\u7845 p, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n ti\'eau t\'e1n trong kh\'f4ng kh\'ed.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4 h\uc0\u7845 p Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t nh\u7865  \u273 i, v\u432 \u417 n tay tr\'e1i ra \u273 em c\u7853 u giam \u7903  trong gh\u7871 , nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i xu\u7889 ng chuy\'ean ch\'fa nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean, n\u7871 u t\'f4i mu\u7889 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ngay b\'e2y gi\u7901  th\'ec sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n h\'f4n l\'ean c\u7857 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "... N\u7871 u t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ch\u7901  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'eam th\'ec sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u417  ng\'e1c nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u432 a ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p, m\u7863 t l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7887  l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7907 i th\'eam n\u7919 a, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y tho\'e1ng c\'e1i \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915  tr\'ean gh\u7871  l\'ean, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "\u272 \u7915 ng nh\'fac nh\'edch, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7897 ng. Nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang \'f4m m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'ed l\u7921 c l\u7899 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \'f4m m\'ecnh l\'ean l\u7847 u, \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , th\u7871  m\'e0 v\u7919 ng v\'e0ng l\'e0m li\u7873 n m\u7897 t m\u7841 ch, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng t\u7889 n ch\'fat s\u7913 c n\'e0o. D\'f9 sao c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh l\'e0 lo\u7841 i h\'ecnh m\u7843 nh mai t\'f9y t\'f9y ti\u7879 n ti\u7879 n c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  nh\u7845 c l\'ean th\u7871  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t c\u7843 m th\u7909  \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, ch\u7881  \u7903  th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7899 i l\'e0m ra ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean khi\u7871 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'e0ng th\'eam \u273 i\'ean cu\u7891 ng. X\'e1c th\u7921 c... kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng l\u7847 n c\'f9ng v\u7899 i th\u7913  kia, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\'f4m qua ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\'ecnh c\u7843 m gi\'e1c sai...\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i l\'e0 b\u7883  c\'e2u n\'f3i tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 c\u7911 a m\'ecnh k\'edch th\'edch hay kh\'f4ng, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\u7847 n n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0m theo \'fd h\u7855 n, kh\'f4ng ch\'fat kh\u7855 c ch\u7871 . Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 m\u7841 nh mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i ra, trong l\'f2ng l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \'e1y n\'e1y thi\u7871 u n\u7907 , \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean t\u7853 n l\u7921 c ph\u7889 i h\u7907 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 l\u259 n qua l\u259 n l\u7841 i r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c qua bao l\'e2u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng s\u7855 p ng\u7845 t, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7915  ph\'eda sau g\u7855 t gao \'f4m l\u7845 y m\'ecnh, c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7865  m\'fat h\'f4n g\'e1y c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p kia, n\u7871 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i d\'e1n b\'ean tai th\'ec g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i mang theo c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\u7887 a m\'e3n r\'f5 r\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n th\uc0\u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t c\u7913 ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng t\u7853 p trung tinh th\u7847 n, m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra, tuy r\u7857 ng th\u7875  x\'e1c v\'e0 tinh th\u7847 n \u273 \u7873 u m\u7879 t m\u7887 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, nh\u432 ng trong m\u7855 t r\u7845 t thanh minh, \'fd lo\u7841 n t\'ecnh m\'ea v\u7915 a r\u7891 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t s\u7841 ch s\u7869 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, v\u7851 n nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\u432  c\u361 , ch\u7881  n\u7895  l\u7921 c duy tr\'ec tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh, kh\u7869  g\u7885 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m c\uc0\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'e0n kh\'e0n nh\u432  c\u361 , mang theo m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i l\u432 u luy\u7871 n tri\u7873 n mi\'ean kh\'e1c, v\u7915 a l\'ean ti\u7871 ng ngay c\u7843  b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng quen .\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 ?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i, c\'e0ng \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7853 u, "B\u7843 o b\u7889 i c\u7853 u c\'f2n t\u7881 nh? Mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\'fac h\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n h\u417 i th\u7903  phun tr\'ean c\u7893  Tr\'ec Di\'ean, mang theo t\u7915 ng tia l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n trong x\u432 \u417 ng c\u7889 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i g\uc0\u7885 i l\'e0 qu\'ea m\u7929  nh\'e2n l\'e0 m\u7897  anh h\'f9ng, c\'f3 l\u7869  d\'f9ng v\u7899 i th\u7913  n\'e0y c\u361 ng th\'edch h\u7907 p, \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\'e1 t\u7853 n h\u7913 ng qu\'e1 th\u7887 a m\'e3n qu\'e1 t\'f9y \'fd, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7929  m\'e3n \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i ngay c\u7843  ng\u7909 y trang m\'ecnh c\u361 ng qu\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\uc0\u417 i th\u7903  c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  l\'e0 lo\u7841 i nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  n\'e0y, d\'f9 c\'f3 l\'e0 tr\u7901 i sinh th\'e2n th\u7875  l\u7841 nh th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\uc0\u7875  qu\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  kia, \u273 \'eam h\'e8 n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 \u7903  Ph\u7853 t \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng trong nh\'e0 ch\'fa, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u v\u7915 a kinh s\u7907  v\u7915 a m\u7879 t m\u7887 i ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i mu\u7889 n ng\u7845 t \u273 i, th\u7913  kia c\u361 ng \'f4m c\u7853 u t\u7915  ph\'eda sau nh\u432  v\u7853 y, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n g\'e1y c\u7853 u, k\'ecm l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  \'97\'97 ngay c\u7843  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\u7887 a m\'e3n sau khi th\u7887 a s\u7913 c mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec th\'ec l\'e0m trong ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i kia c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'fac.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7849 y v\'f2ng \'f4m c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ra ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, ch\u7841 y xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng. Qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a c\u7853 u to\'e0n b\u7897  b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'e9m t\u7913  t\'e1n d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p nh\u7863 t, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p m\u7903  t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\u7899  m\u7897 t b\u7897  v\u7897 i v\'e3 m\u7863 c l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac n\'e0y ch\'ednh l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m t\'ednh t\'ecnh t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t t\u432  duy ch\u7853 m nh\u7845 t, nhu t\'ecnh m\u7853 t \'fd ng\u7853 p tr\'e0n trong m\u7855 t qu\u7843  th\u7921 c kh\'f4ng n\u417 i \u273 \u7875  ch\u7913 a, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'f2i h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n tr\u259 ng mu\u7889 n sao h\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\u7905  c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 ang th\'e2n m\u7853 t l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u273 \u7849 y ra th\u7853 t s\u7921  ng\'e2y ng\u7849 n c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i, h\u7855 n ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7843 o m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 nhanh ch\'f3ng m\u7863 c xong qu\u7847 n \'e1o, m\u7897 t b\u7897  d\'e1ng mu\u7889 n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n ch\u432 a ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p, ch\u7881  tr\u7847 m gi\u7885 ng k\'eau t\'ean \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: "A Di\'ean, l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? L\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n lu\'f4n quay l\u432 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda h\u7855 n, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7881 nh \u273 \u7889 n th\u7887 a \u273 \'e1ng, c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7845 t v\'e0o trong t\'fai m\u7899 i quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i li\u7871 c nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, sau \u273 \'f3 d\'f9ng t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  b\'ecnh sinh nhanh nh\u7845 t ch\u7841 y ra kh\u7887 i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \'97\'97 trong nh\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 , l\'fac Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m h\u7855 n \u273 i v\'e0o, ngay c\u7843  c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7853 m r\'e3i tr\u7847 m m\u7863 t xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n t\u7915  trong c\'e1i li\u7871 c m\u7855 t v\u7915 a r\u7891 i khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7907  h\'e3i \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i h\u7855 n\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, h\u7841  m\'ed m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
