\cb3 "C\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i, " Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e2n nh\u7855 c t\'ecm t\u7915 , kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean n\'f3i r\'f5 v\u7899 i m\u7865  m\'ecnh nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, "Ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7853 u ta kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7889 t."\cb1 \
