\cb3 L\uc0\u432 u Ph\u432 \u7907 ng O\'e1nh th\u7903  d\'e0i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean \'e0, sau khi hai \u273 \u7913 a \u273 i m\u7865  c\'f2n n\'f3i v\u7899 i cha con, \u273 \u7873 u do ch\'fang ta chi\u7873 u con qu\'e1 m\u7913 c r\u7891 i, mu\u7889 n t\'ecm m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7883 n con nu\'f4ng chi\u7873 u con th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng. Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  chung s\u7869  ph\u7843 i ma s\'e1t l\u7851 n nhau, nh\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7883 n nhau, m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i d\'e0i \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 , v\u7915 a nh\u7853 n chu\u7849 n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 li\u7873 n \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n ch\u7889 i b\u7887  h\u7855 n. M\u7865  v\'e0 cha \u273 \u7873 u th\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kia r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec th\'ec con v\u7899 i c\u7853 u ta n\'ean n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng v\u7899 i nhau."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe c\'f3 ch\'fat s\uc0\u7919 ng s\u7901 : "Me\u803  n\'f3i g\'ec c\u417 ?"\cb1 \
