\cb3 C\'f4 ch\uc0\u7853 m r\'e3i, t\u7915 ng ch\'fat t\u7915 ng ch\'fat ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u7865  tay \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean l\u7891 ng ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a c\'f4 ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, c\'f4 th\u7845 y n\u417 i c\u7893  Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng d\u7845 u t\'edch s\u7855 c di\u7877 m n\u7889 i th\'e0nh m\u7897 t v\u7879 t, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\u7897  ra n\'e9t m\u7863 t o\'e1n h\u7853 n kh\u7893  s\u7903 : "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i n\'e0y \u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y ch\u7881  \u7903  b\'ean em \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai kh\'e1c h\uc0\u7871 t, th\u7913  kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i. D\'f9 c\'f3 l\'e0 l\u7901 i th\u7873  m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i b\'ean nhau, c\u361 ng l\'e0 \u432 ng thu\u7853 n v\u7899 i th\u7913  kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 l\uc0\u7921 c kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, d\'e1n v\'e0o c\u7917 a tr\u432 \u7907 t ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, m\u7863 t c\u361 ng t\u7921 a l\'ean c\u7917 a, quay \u273 \u7847 u \u273 i kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn t\'e0 v\u7853 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch qu\u7923  xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t theo c\u7853 u, tay \u273 \'e8 l\'ean ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u, ng\u7849 ng m\u7863 t ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, trong m\u7855 t l\'e0 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m s\'e2u \u273 \u7853 m kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nh\u7847 m l\u7851 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, em th\'edch anh m\'e0, v\uc0\u7853 y n\'ean... cho em tim c\u7911 a anh \u273 i, nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\'e1t hi\uc0\u7879 n m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, to\'e0n th\'e2n c\u361 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  m\u7897 t s\u7907 i d\'e2y th\u7915 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c giam c\u7847 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Y\uc0\u7871 t h\u7847 u c\u7853 u c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7897 ng hai c\'e1i, tr\u417  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p nhu t\'ecnh ch\u7853 m r\'e3i d\u7921 a \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean vai ph\u7843 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, d\u432 \u7899 i tay th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n d\'f9ng l\u7921 c, si\u7871 t v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i ch\u7871 t \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n nh\u432  th\u7871 , trong \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  l\'f3e l\'ean t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 qua, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t \'e2n c\u7847 n c\u7911 a cha m\u7865 , b\u7841 n b\'e8 vui v\u7867  t\u432 \u417 i c\u432 \u7901 i, c\'f9ng v\u7899 i... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\'e1i \'f4m, n\u7909  h\'f4n, l\u7901 i y\'eau, t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng th\u7875  nghi\u7879 m y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y, to\'e0n b\u7897  li\'ean quan t\u7899 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 g\u7841 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 b\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u7881  d\'e1m ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 i ch\u7871 t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7845 t v\u7845 n, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \'f2i m\u7897 t c\'e2u gi\u7843 i th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi..."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7849 m b\u7849 m trong l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u t\'f4i bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927 , vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean l\'e0m s\u7869  l\'e0 tr\u7903  v\u7873  t\'ecm c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bi\uc0\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927  r\u7891 i, t\'f4i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng s\u7907  c\u7853 u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 m\u7897 t th\u7913  k\'ec qu\'e1i, nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i trong nh\u7919 ng c\u7889  s\u7921  *ch\'ed qu\'e1i kia, r\'f5 r\'e0ng khi c\'f2n s\u7889 ng nhu nh\u432 \u7907 c v\'f4 l\u7921 c, b\u7883  b\u7913 c \'e9p kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o ph\u7843 n kh\'e1ng, kh\'f4ng n\u417 i \u273 \u7875  tr\u7889 n, sau khi ch\u7871 t h\'f3a th\'e0nh l\u7879  qu\u7927  r\u7891 i l\u7841 i d\'e1m \u273 i t\'ecm \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'f2i m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (ch\'ed qu\'e1i: ghi ch\'e9p nh\uc0\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n qu\'e1i d\u7883 )
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  sau khi ch\u7871 t, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng s\u7907  h\'e3i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n ch\u7871 t, c\u7853 u s\u7907  qu\u7927 , s\u7907  C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, s\u7907  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, x\'e9t \u273 \u7871 n c\'f9ng, c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 s\u7907  ch\u7871 t m\'e0 th\'f4i, c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n s\u7889 ng m\'e0 th\'f4i, c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  k\u7923  qu\'e1i kia d\u7877  d\'e0ng c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 o\u7841 t quy\u7873 n l\u7907 i sinh t\u7891 n c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd th\uc0\u7913 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ra s\u7913 c gi\u7857 ng co, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7897 ng. C\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 ng tay, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f9ng l\'fac \uc0\u273 \'f3, C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  m\u7897 t l\u7921 c m\u7841 nh \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n b\'f3p ch\u259 \u803 t c\u7893  k\'e9o l\'ean, kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng b\u7883  k\'e9o ng\u432 \u7907 c v\u7873  ph\'eda sau. M\u7863 t c\'f4 tr\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng, t\u7913  chi kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng gi\'e3y d\u7909 a, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i gi\'e3y kh\'f4ng ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean m\uc0\u7843 nh \u273 \u7845 t tr\u7889 ng ph\'eda sau C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t th\'e2n \u7843 nh cao g\u7847 y th\u7859 ng t\u7855 p, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  h\u417 i nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u, nh\'ecn c\'f4 b\u7883  k\'e9o \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh m\u7899 i d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kinh ng\uc0\u7841 c nh\'ecn m\u7897 t m\'e0n n\'e0y, th\u7917  m\u7845 y l\u7847 n, nh\u432 ng kh\'ed l\u7921 c \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ng\u7891 i \u273 \'f3 nh\'ecn.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n kia, l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7841  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn y\'eau v\u7853 t kho\'e1c da thi\u7871 u n\u7919  xinh \u273 \u7865 p tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i cong kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng, ng\u7919  kh\'ed c\u7921 c nh\u7865  n\'f3i v\u7899 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch: "Ng\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m l\u7847 n b\u7843 y l\u432 \u7907 t xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t ta, ta kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd ng\u432 \u417 i, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u417 i li\u7873 n cho r\u7857 ng ta kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u417 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7875  m\u7863 c n\'f3, l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec h\u7855 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y A Di\'ean \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i n\'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\u7843 o c\u7843 m \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, tr\'e1i l\u7841 i l\u7841 i b\u7903 i v\'ec s\u7921  xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n c\u7911 a n\'f3 m\'e0 c\'e0ng th\'eam \u7927  l\u7841 i k\u7873  c\u7853 n m\'ecnh; v\u7873  sau \u273 \u7875  m\u7863 c n\'f3, l\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng m\'ecnh ra tay s\u7869  \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  d\u7845 u v\u7871 t, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i b\u7883  A Di\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u d\'f9 sao h\'f4m nay h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 b\u7841 i l\u7897 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\u7921 c k\u7923  kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c uy hi\u7871 p c\u7921 c l\u7899 n, d\u7889 c s\u7913 c li\u7873 u m\u7841 ng l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t c\'e2u, kh\'f4ng xu\u7845 t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \'e2m n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u432 \u417 i l\'e2y d\'ednh t\'e0 kh\'ed v\'e0 \'e1i \'fd c\u7911 a ta, m\u7841 o danh ta, d\'f9ng b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y, m\u417  t\u432 \u7903 ng, ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a ta, ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f2n t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng ta c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7887  qua cho ng\u432 \u417 i?" M\u7895 i m\u7897 t t\u7897 i ... \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tha th\u7913 .\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (\'e1i \'fd: t\'ecnh c\uc0\u7843 m, y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Di\'ean b\uc0\u7843 o b\u7889 i, Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, b\u7903 i \u273 \u7875  c\'f3 th\u7875  danh ch\'ednh ng\'f4n thu\u7853 n k\u7871 t l\'e0m phu th\'ea v\u7899 i b\u7843 o b\u7889 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n n\'ean m\u7899 i l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n nh\'e2n v\u7853 t n\u7919 , th\u7871  nh\u432 ng g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \'f3, b\u7897  d\'e1ng \u273 \'f3, r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 d\u7921 a theo ng\u432 \u7901 i trong l\'f2ng h\u7855 n ng\'e0y nh\u7899  \u273 \'eam mong m\'e0 t\u7841 o ra. C\'f4 ta sao d\'e1m li\u7873 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y quang minh ch\'ednh \u273 \u7841 i \u273 eo l\'ean c\'e1i b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y, l\u7845 y danh ngh\u297 a c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \'fd \u273 \u7891  c\'e2u d\u7851 n?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, du\u7895 i tay n\'e9m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng sang b\u7913 c t\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean kia, ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng va \u273 \u7853 p c\u7921 c l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... To gan l\uc0\u7899 n m\u7853 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\'e2n th\u7875  ph\'e0m thai, c\'e1c kh\u7899 p x\u432 \u417 ng b\u7883  va \u273 \u7853 p sai kh\u7899 p, th\'e2n th\u7875  v\u7905  v\u7909 n th\'e0nh t\u7915 ng kh\u7889 i, nh\u432 ng k\u7923  d\u7883  l\'e0 n\'f3 l\u7841 i h\u7907 p l\u7841 i th\'e0nh m\u7897 t th\u7875  nh\u432  c\u361 , ch\u7881  l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y v\u7871 t r\u7841 n \u7903  gi\u7919 a, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\'fap b\'ea s\u7913  b\u7883  n\'e9m v\u7905  h\u7907 p l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 'C\'f4 ta' n\uc0\u7857 m s\u7845 p, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t g\u7909 c tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, m\u7903  l\u7899 n \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u \u273 en nh\'ecn nam nh\'e2n \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, trong m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i to\'e1t ra ho\u7843 ng s\u7907  v\'e0 kinh s\u7907  c\u7921 c \u273 \u7897 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Y\'eau v\uc0\u7853 t h\u7841 i m\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, t\'e0n nh\u7851 n \u273 \u7871 n c\u7921 c \u273 i\u7875 m, to\'e0n th\'e2n d\'ednh \u273 \u7847 y huy\u7871 t s\'e1t nh\u432  th\u7871 , v\u7853 y m\'e0 c\u361 ng s\u7869  s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u7899 n l\u7841 nh d\'e2ng l\'ean, c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 g\uc0\u7885 i l\'e0 "L\'e2y d\'ednh t\'e0 kh\'ed v\'e0 \'e1i \'fd c\u7911 a ta", C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, t\u7915  m\u7897 t nh\'e2n v\u7853 t tr\'f2 ch\u417 i v\'f4 tri v\'f4 th\u7913 c h\'f3a th\'e0nh t\'e0 y\'eau, h\'f3a ra l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec h\u7855 n sao? C\'f4 ta \'f4m t\'ecnh c\u7843 m b\u7879 nh tr\u7841 ng c\u7889  ch\u7845 p kh\'f3 m\'e0 hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\u7841 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\'ecnh s\'e2u nh\u432  bi\u7875 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec m\'ecnh l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7907 ng phu c\u7911 a 'Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i' trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i, m\'e0 c\u361 ng l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec h\u7855 n sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'e1ch kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c, tr\'e1ch kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903  trong c\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3, b\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n "Ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7913  ba" nh\u432  trong l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n th\u7893 i... Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7913  kia \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, m\'e0 l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec h\u7855 n cho t\u7899 i nay, v\u7851 n quang minh ch\'ednh \u273 \u7841 i s\u7889 ng c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u t\u7899 i cu\u7889 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7855 n c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh l\'fac n\'e3y C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch v\u7915 a ng\u7853 p tr\'e0n nhu t\'ecnh ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn m\'ecnh v\u7915 a n\'f3i "Em th\'edch anh m\'e0, n\'ean cho em tim c\u7911 a anh \u273 i", c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u run r\u7849 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7855 n r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c mu\u7889 n l\'e0m c\'e1i g\'ec? H\u7855 n c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n tim c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u432  ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ti\u7871 n l\'ean m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 i t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u432 \u7901 i C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch li\'ean t\u7909 c gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a m\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Ch\'e2n h\u7855 n b\u432 \u7899 c r\u7845 t nh\u7865 , l\'fac \u273 \u7897 ng g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t ra \'e2m thanh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ch\u7853 m r\'e3i c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i, h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda th\'e2n th\u7875  \u273 ang treo l\u417  l\u7917 ng c\u7911 a C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \u432 a tay ra.\cb1 \
