\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean gh\u7871  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh th\u7843  xu\u7889 ng, tay ph\u7843 i ch\u7889 ng tr\'ean th\'e0nh gh\u7871 , c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng nh\u432  c\'f3 nh\u432  kh\'f4ng l\u7841 i li\'ean mi\'ean kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng h\'f4n c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f3c... V\u7851 n s\u7907  t\'f4i nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u432 ?" H\u7855 n th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\u7881  non, h\'f4n l\'ean gi\u7885 t n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t tr\'ean kh\'f3e m\u7855 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7917 a ph\'f2ng trong t\'edch t\u7855 c \u273 \'f3 b\u7883  ph\'e1 ra, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac, ung dung \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n t\u7889 t quan t\'e2m b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh mang theo Ti\u7875 u An ph\'e1 c\u7917 a v\'e0o, d\'f2 x\'e9t xung quanh m\u7897 t phen, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \'e2u r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "... \uc0\u7902  \u273 \'f3." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7881  th\u7913  m\'e0u \u273 en tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  chim s\u7907  c\'e0nh cong \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 H\u7891  Tinh, "Ch\u7883  l\'e0 ai, v\'e0o b\u7857 ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m xu\u7889 ng kinh ng\u7841 c xem x\'e9t ch\u7845 t l\u7887 ng m\'e0u \u273 en C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch l\u432 u l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean nghi ng\u7901  l\u7849 m b\u7849 m: "N\'f3 c\'e1i d\u7841 ng n\'e0y, h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 b\u7883  t\'e0 kh\'ed c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i h\u417 n ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  r\u7891 i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7883  ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'fap \u7903  trong gh\u7871  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u7845 n kinh qu\'e1 \u273 \u7897 , l\u7841 i nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 ang v\'f4 c\'f9ng \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng, m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u n\'f3i: "T\'f4i l\'e0 H\u7891  Tinh, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 s\u432  \u273 \u7879  c\u7911 a t\'f4i, Ti\u7875 u An, b\u7885 n t\'f4i l\'e0 b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u ta c\'f3 nguy c\u417  g\u7863 p nguy hi\u7875 m n\'ean \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y b\u7843 o v\u7879  c\u7853 u \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec mu\uc0\u7889 n l\u7845 y t\'edn nhi\u7879 m c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, ch\u7883  c\u7889  \'fd n\'f3i: "T\'f4i bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u t\'ean Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, l\'e0 b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\'f3 quan h\u7879  r\u7845 t t\u7889 t v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \u7845 y, hai c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  c\'f9ng nhau. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i c\u7853 u v\u7899 i t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e2u n\'f3i sau c\'f9ng khi\uc0\u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\'f5 r\'e0ng d\u7883 u l\u7841 i th\u7847 n s\u7855 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh th\u7845 y th\u7871  kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "V\u7853 y Di\u7879 p \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7885 c, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t v\u7915 a x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7841  m\u7855 t, v\u7851 n l\'e0 b\u7897  d\u7841 ng lu\u7889 ng cu\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao: "S\'e1ng h\'f4m nay t\'f4i v\'e0 A Di\'ean x\u7843 y ra m\'e2u thu\u7851 n, c\u7853 u \u7845 y t\u7915  nh\'e0 t\'f4i t\u7921  m\'ecnh ch\u7841 y v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c, trong l\'f2ng t\'f4i th\u7845 y th\u7865 n, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 l\u7895 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \u7845 y n\'ean v\u7897 i l\'e1i xe \u273 u\u7893 i theo. K\u7871 t qu\u7843  t\'f4i v\u7915 a m\u7899 i v\'e0o k\'fd t\'fac ch\u432 a bao l\'e2u, c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i A Di\'ean th\'ec C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \'e3 xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 ang g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\u7899 i t\'f4i." H\u7891  Tinh n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\'ec ra l\'e0 ch\uc0\u7883 ." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn ch\u7883  m\u7897 t c\'e1i, g\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u "T\'f4i ch\u7881  th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u7845 y \u273 ang g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 ai."\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec tr\u432 \u7899 c kia C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\u361 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean \u273 \u7871 n k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 t\'ecm A Di\'ean, cho n\'ean tuy r\u7857 ng t\'f4i kh\'f4ng th\'edch c\'f4 ta nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  \'fd, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i l\u7847 n n\'e0y A Di\'ean sau khi g\u7863 p c\'f4 ta r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'f3 v\u7867  r\u7845 t lo l\u7855 ng s\u7907  h\'e3i, li\'ean t\u7909 c nh\'ecn t\'f4i, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7871 n c\u7841 nh t\'f4i tr\u7889 n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m. T\'f4i tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7851 n ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, ch\u7907 t th\u7845 y C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t A Di\'ean, \u273 \'e8 tay l\'ean ng\u7921 c tr\'e1i A Di\'ean. Sau \u273 \'f3 t\u7915  ng\u7921 c tr\'e1i c\u7853 u \u7845 y \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tu\'f4n ra m\u7897 t d\'f2ng kh\'ed \u273 en, v\'e2y C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch l\u7841 i... R\u7891 i c\'f4 ta li\u7873 n bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh c\'e1i d\u7841 ng n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i, tr\'ean m\u7863 t l\u7897  ra th\u7847 n s\u7855 c ngh\u297  l\u7841 i m\'e0 s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\'ec ra l\'e0 th\uc0\u7871 ." H\u7891  Tinh \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 c\u7853 u t\u7881  m\u7881 , t\u7921  nh\u7911 , "Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  l\'e0 b\u7883  t\'e0 kh\'ed b\u7849 m sinh trong c\u417  th\u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  r\u7891 i? Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 t\u7841 i sao c\u7843 m gi\'e1c t\'e0 kh\'ed trong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u l\u7841 i d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c h\u417 n so v\u7899 i l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c g\u7863 p nh\u7881 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7883  l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u tr\'e1nh ra, c\'f9ng Ti\u7875 u An hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7845 y l\'e1 b\'f9a \u273 em ch\u7845 t l\u7887 ng m\'e0u \u273 en tr\'ean s\'e0n nh\'e0 to\'e0n b\u7897  h\'fat v\'e0o trong l\'e1 b\'f9a, l\u7841 i thu t\u7845 t c\u7843  l\'e1 b\'f9a b\u7887  v\'e0o trong m\u7897 t b\'ecnh s\u7913 , ni\'eam phong n\u7855 p. M\u7845 y th\u7913  n\'e0y b\u7885 n h\u7885  mang v\u7873  x\u7917  l\'fd ti\u7871 p, b\u7845 t k\u7875  n\'f3i th\u7871  n\'e0o, tuy r\u7857 ng nghe v\'e0o tai c\'f3 ch\'fat k\u7923  qu\'e1i, nh\u432 ng \'edt nh\u7845 t C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t, nguy\'ean nh\'e2n c\u7909  th\u7875  v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c nghi\'ean c\u7913 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7902  \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng sao n\u7919 a, nh\u432 ng \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7911 a th\u7843 m \'e1n li\'ean ho\'e0n l\u432 u l\u7841 i v\u7851 n c\'f2n, v\u7851 n c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n ch\u7901  ch\u7883  \u273 i x\u7917  l\'fd. H\u7891  Tinh c\'f3 ch\'fat lo l\u7855 ng li\u7871 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gh\u7871 , t\u7915  khi ch\u7883  xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n l\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c, kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7883  quay \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean: "L\'e0m phi\u7873 n c\u7853 u ch\u259 m s\'f3c Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec, trong kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u7845 y c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7883 u kh\'f4ng \'edt kinh h\'e3i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e1p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c: "\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 vi\u7879 c t\'f4i n\'ean l\'e0m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng \u273 ang l\'fac ch\u7883  \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7841 nh c\u7917 a, Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7891 i l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  kinh \u273 \u7897 ng, tay ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7863 t \u7903  b\'ean \u273 \'f9i im \u7855 ng n\u7855 m l\u7841 i hai c\'e1i, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng g\u7885 i ch\u7883  l\u7841 i, thanh \'e2m y\u7871 u \u7899 t, c\'f2n mang theo m\u7897 t ch\'fat kh\'e0n kh\'e0n: "H\u7891  t\u7927 ..."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 c\u417  h\u7897 i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u \u273 en c\u7911 a c\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng H\u7891  Tinh: "H\u7891  t\u7927 , ch\u7883  n\'f3i b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a em l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e2u h\uc0\u7887 i n\'e0y ph\u7889 i h\u7907 p v\u7899 i s\u7855 c m\u7863 t h\u417 i t\'e1i nh\u7907 t suy y\u7871 u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, c\'f3 lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c k\u7923  l\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \'e1nh m\uc0\u7855 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\'f3 ch\u7901  mong v\'e0 c\u7847 u kh\u7849 n r\u7845 t nh\u7841 t, nh\u432 ng H\u7891  Tinh nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7883  li\u7871 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \'e1y n\'e1y c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, l\u7841 i chuy\u7875 n h\u432 \u7899 ng sang Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec, kh\'f4ng n\'ean nghi th\u7847 n nghi qu\u7927 , d\u7841 o n\'e0y c\u7853 u b\u7883  s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n cho\'e1ng v\'e1ng r\u7891 i. B\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u h\u7855 n sao c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7913 ? Y\'ean t\'e2m \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\'e1 to mi\uc0\u7879 ng, h\u417 i h\u417 i quay \u273 \u7847 u, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  khung c\u7917 a, m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, con m\u7855 t m\'e0u \u273 en th\'e2m tr\u7847 m, n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i \'f4n nhu.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai tay c\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t th\'e0nh quy\u7873 n, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng n\'f3i: "C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch l\'e0 b\u7883  h\u7855 n di\u7879 t tr\u7915  \u273 \u7845 y, em \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y t\u7853 n m\u7855 t." H\u7855 n v\u7915 a r\u7891 i... t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 l\u7915 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh tr\u7845 n an \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n c\u7853 u, v\u7895  v\u7895  vai c\u7853 u: "... C\u7853 u l\'e0 s\u7907  qu\'e1 m\u7913 c, sinh ra \u7843 o gi\'e1c r\u7891 i. B\'e2y gi\u7901  ph\u7843 i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i cho t\u7889 t, t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'e0 \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i cho khu\'e2y kh\u7887 a \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7855 c h\u7859 n \u7903  trong m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7853 u r\u7845 t kh\'f3 ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n s\u7921  th\u7853 t t\'e0 kh\'ed c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch. Th\u7871  nh\u432 ng t\'e0 kh\'ed tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u l\'e0 tr\u7901 i sinh \u273 \u7845 y, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\u7895 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\u7897 i \'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Th\u7853 t c\'f3 l\u7895 i, l\'e0m phi\u7873 n c\u7853 u c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ch\u259 m s\'f3c Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec th\u7853 t t\u7889 t, \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m l\u7901 i c\u7853 u \u7845 y n\'f3i. Hy v\u7885 ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u c\u7853 u \u7845 y n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 c\'f3 th\'e0nh ki\u7871 n hay \'e1c \'fd v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, ch\u7881  l\'e0 trong kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u7845 y qu\'e1 c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng tr\u432 \u417 ng qu\'e1 s\u7907  h\'e3i n\'ean m\u7899 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u \u7845 y t\'edn nhi\u7879 m nh\u7845 t \u7927  l\u7841 i nh\u7845 t. Ki\'ean nh\u7851 n khai th\'f4ng th\u7857 ng b\'e9, qua th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y s\u7869  t\u7889 t th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Lo\uc0\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i g\u7863 p b\'e1c s\u297  t\'e2m l\'fd, b\u7903 i v\'ec b\'e1c s\u297  t\'e2m l\'fd ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tin t\u432 \u7903 ng nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927  l\'e0m lo\u7841 n c\u7853 u n\'f3i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  g\u7917 i g\u7855 m hi v\u7885 ng v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\'f9ng c\u7853 u tr\u7843 i qua nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y tr\u7907  gi\'fap.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c "C\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u \u7845 y t\'edn nhi\u7879 m nh\u7845 t \u7927  l\u7841 i nh\u7845 t", \'e1nh m\u7855 t ch\u7907 t l\'f3e, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e1p: "T\'f4i hi\u7875 u, t\'f4i s\u7869  ch\u259 m s\'f3c A Di\'ean th\u7853 t t\u7889 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ti\u7877 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ra c\u7917 a, nh\'ecn b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i xa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng tho\'e1ng c\'e1i l\'e2m v\'e0o y\'ean t\uc0\u297 nh, ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\'e2y ra ng\uc0\u7891 i \u273 \'f3, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t \u273 i tia hy v\u7885 ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng. Gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i c\u7847 u c\u7913 u c\u7843 nh s\'e1t, c\u7843 nh s\'e1t ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i t\u7921  tay \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u giao tr\u7903  l\u7841 i tay hung th\u7911 , n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7889 t, c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i ngoan ngo\'e3n theo h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7841  m\u7855 t kh\'f3a c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a tr\u7903  v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng nghe l\u7901 i. C\u7853 u mu\u7889 n \'f4ng x\'e3 b\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\u7855 t \u273 i sao? A Di\'ean c\u7911 a t\'f4i \u273 \'e2y ch\u7859 ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 mu\u7889 n *th\u7911  ho\u7841 t qu\u7843  \u432 ? T\'f4i sao c\'f3 th\u7875  cam l\'f2ng?"\cb1 \
