\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay m\uc0\u7863 t \u273 i, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u, tay h\u417 i run, m\u7897 t m\u7855 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9ng tay tr\'e1i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng n\'e2ng m\u7863 t c\u7853 u l\'ean, d\'f9ng ch\'f3p m\u361 i v\'e0 m\'f4i vu\u7889 t ve: "A Di\'ean, c\u7853 u nh\'ecn t\'f4i \u273 i, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn t\'f4i... L\'e0 t\'f4i sai r\u7891 i, n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i kh\'f4ng n\'ean qu\'e1 n\'f3ng v\u7897 i." \u272 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i d\'f9ng tay ph\u7843 i n\u7855 m hai tay c\u7853 u, gi\u7919  \u7903  trong tay m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u259 m \u273 \'f3 qu\u7843  nhi\'ean c\u361 ng l\'e0 h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u259 n b\u7843 n ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c sai.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2u ph\u7843 i l\'e0 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  qu\'e1 n\'f3ng v\u7897 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, c\u7893  h\u7885 ng b\u7895 ng \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9ng ch\'f3p m\u361 i d\'e1n l\'ean ch\'f3p m\u361 i c\u7853 u, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\u7899  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'f3: "... Nh\u432 ng t\'f4i v\u7915 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u, t\'f4i li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng kh\u7855 c ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. T\'f4i v\u7915 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u, t\'f4i li\u7873 n bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u l\'e0 c\u7911 a t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "A Di\'ean, c\uc0\u7853 u thu\u7897 c v\u7873  t\'f4i. Tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\'f3 kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i... D\'f9 n\u7871 u c\'f3 ki\u7871 p tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng thu\u7897 c v\u7873  t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7911 a t\'f4i, c\u7911 a t\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n bao l\'e2u, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng cho r\u7901 i \u273 i, ai c\u361 ng \u273 \u7915 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i s\uc0\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7853 u." H\u7855 n d\u7883 u d\'e0ng th\'ec th\u7847 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u m\u7903  m\u7855 t. C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 "Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, em th\'edch anh, em s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m h\u7841 i anh, n\'ean anh cho em tim c\u7911 a anh \u273 i, ch\'fang ta s\u7869  v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895 " . Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u. S\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i \u273 \u7891 ng d\u7841 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, sao c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'fd l\u7869  v\'e0 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  h\'f4n kh\u7869  li\u7871 m m\'ed m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u7881  h\u417 i tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh, l\'f4ng mi run r\u7849 y, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra nh\'ecn m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7847 n n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  hi\u7879 n ra m\u7897 t tia m\u7901  m\u7883 t m\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh h\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng gi\u7843  v\u7901 . H\u7855 n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, \'f4m ngang Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, \u273 i th\u7859 ng ra ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra, t\u7915  g\'f3c \u273 \u7897  n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\'ean m\u7863 t nam nh\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... \uc0\u272 i \u273 \'e2u?" Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng h\u7887 i. Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mu\u7889 n c\u7913  \'f4m c\u7853 u \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i v\u7899 i b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p nh\u432  v\u7853 y k\'e9o c\u7917 a \u273 i ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 ang l\'e0 gi\u7919 a tr\u432 a, b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i khung c\u7843 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i nh\u432  trong t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, m\'e0 l\'e0 tr\u7889 ng tr\u7843 i \u273 \u7871 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n y\'ean t\u297 nh, gi\u7889 ng v\u7899 i c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch t\u7841 o ra khi v\'e2y c\u7853 u \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t tay \'e1o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, \'f4m th\u7859 ng c\u7853 u ra b\'e3i \u273 \u7895  xe, nh\'e9t c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong xe c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, th\u7855 t ch\u7863 t d\'e2y an to\'e0n. Sau khi ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n s\'e2n bay \u7903  v\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i \'f4 l\u7841 i k\'e9o c\u7853 u l\'ean m\'e1y bay.\cb1 \
\cb3 "R\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec?" C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch mu\u7889 n m\u7841 ng c\u7853 u, c\u361 ng ch\u7881  \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng gi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7845 y tim l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, h\'e0 t\u7845 t c\'f2n mu\u7889 n l\'ean tr\u7901 i?\cb1 \
\cb3 "A Di\'ean, c\uc0\u7853 u ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c \u273 i, ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i v\'e0o bu\u7891 ng l\'e1i, "Ch\'fang ta \u273 i l\'e0m th\u7911  t\u7909 c k\u7871 t h\'f4n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi th\u7853 t s\u7921  b\u7883  k\'e9o v\'e0o ph\'f2ng \u273 \u259 ng k\'ed k\u7871 t h\'f4n n\u432 \u7899 c C v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7915 ng nh\'e1o, ngay c\u7843  visa t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\'e0!"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e0ng th\'eam qu\uc0\u7927  d\u7883  l\'e0, m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i t\u7899 i n\'e0y c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\u7897 t sinh v\u7853 t n\'e0o, kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  ng\u432 \u7901 i, ngay c\u7843  con chim con ki\u7871 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7889 ng v\u7855 ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7875  \'fd m\u7845 y th\u7913  \u273 \'f3, " Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\'e1y m\'f3c, l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7881 m, "T\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u259 n c\'e1ch ch\'fang ta v\'e0 to\'e0n b\u7897  nh\u7919 ng sinh m\u7879 nh kh\'e1c, ch\'fang ta kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  hi\u7879 n h\u7919 u c\u7911 a h\u7885 , b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  hi\u7879 n h\u7919 u c\u7911 a ch\'fang ta. Ch\u7901  l\'e0m xong chuy\u7879 n ch\'fang ta mu\u7889 n l\'e0m, ch\'fang ta l\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng d\'f9ng lo\u7841 i n\u259 ng l\u7921 c n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c "C\'f4 ta" ch\u7881  ng\u259 n c\'e1ch m\u7897 t c\u259 n ph\'f2ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ng\u259 n c\'e1ch to\'e0n b\u7897  th\u7871  gi\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'e1ch kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng l\'e0m gi\u7843  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i th\'e2n ph\u7853 n cho m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi b\uc0\u7853 n r\u7897 n m\u7897 t l\'e1t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 a m\u7897 t gi\u7845 y ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n b\u7857 ng da m\'e0u \u273 en qua: "\u7914 m, gi\u7845 y \u273 \u259 ng k\'ed k\u7871 t h\'f4n, c\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7917  \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, trong \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t ch\u7899 p \u273 \u7897 ng \'e1nh s\'e1ng vui v\u7867  l\u7841 i mong ng\'f3ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i v\'f4 th\u7913 c lui v\u7873  sau m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh s\'e1ng trong m\uc0\u7855 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tho\'e1ng \u7843 m \u273 \u7841 m xu\u7889 ng: "T\'f4i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng cha m\u7865  c\u7853 u s\u7869  c\'f9ng c\u7853 u k\u7871 t th\'e0nh quan h\u7879  h\u7907 p ph\'e1p. A Di\'ean, con ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng b\u7841 n \u273 \u7901 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, t\'f4i cho r\u7857 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  tin t\u432 \u7903 ng t\'f4i, tha th\u7913  cho t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 M\uc0\u7899 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i. D\'f9 c\'f3 l\'e0 con ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec c\u361 ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n v\u7907  s\'e1t h\u7841 i ch\u7891 ng, ch\u7891 ng m\u432 u h\u7841 i v\u7907 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\u297  v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra mi\u7879 ng m\'e0 h\u7887 i m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, chuy\u7879 n C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch... c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Bi\uc0\u7871 t "c\'f4 ta" l\'e0 nhi\u7877 m t\'e0 kh\'ed m\'e0 c\u7911 a m\'ecnh sinh th\'e0nh y\'eau t\'e0 t\'e0n nh\u7851 n, bi\u7871 t "c\'f4 ta" s\u7869  gi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng ch\'fat nh\'e2n t\'ednh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Bi\uc0\u7871 t m\u7897 t ch\'fat." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7841  m\u7855 t, "... Nh\u432 ng n\'f3 t\u7841 o nghi\u7879 t, sao c\'f3 th\u7875  quy l\'ean \u273 \u7847 u t\'f4i? D\'f9 n\'f3 l\'e0 v\'ec t\'e0 kh\'ed c\u7911 a t\'f4i m\'e0 sinh, t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m gi\'e1m th\u7883  n\'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "T\'f4i v\u7899 i n\'f3, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng c\'f9ng m\u7897 t d\u7841 ng. A Di\'ean, t\'f4i mu\u7889 n t\'e2m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n, t\'f4i c\u361 ng s\u7869 , kh\'f4ng h\u7873  gi\u7919  l\u7841 i m\'e0 \u273 em to\'e0n b\u7897  t\'e2m c\u7911 a m\'ecnh cho c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\'e2y ng\uc0\u7889 c \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t m\u7855 t \u273 \u7889 i m\u7855 t nh\'ecn nhau, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7853 y, c\u361 ng qu\'ean m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ng\uc0\u7921 c c\'f3 m\u7897 t thanh \'e2m \u273 ang h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nghe r\'f5, ch\u7881  l\'e0 b\u7843 n n\u259 ng mu\u7889 n t\u7899 i g\u7847 n, t\u7899 i g\u7847 n th\u7871  gi\u7899 i m\'eanh m\'f4ng n\'e0y, tr\u7915  m\'ecnh ra, ch\u7881  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i duy nh\u7845 t m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ti\u7871 n l\'ean ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, k\'e9o c\u7853 u \'f4m th\u7853 t ch\u7863 t v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c: "A Di\'ean, c\u7853 u x\'e1c th\u7921 c t\u7915 ng c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c y\'eau t\'e0 qu\u7845 n th\'e2n \u432 ? Tuy r\u7857 ng \'edch k\u7927 , nh\u432 ng t\u7915  nay v\u7873  sau, t\'f4i s\u7869 , lu\'f4n qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i x\uc0\u7841 o. R\'f5 r\'e0ng t\u7915  n\u259 m n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 qu\u7845 n l\'ean t\'f4i r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean y\'ean l\uc0\u7863 ng nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, t\u7915 ng ch\'fat t\u7915 ng ch\'fat d\u7921 a l\'ean vai \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao t\'f4i c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7841 y kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao t\'f4i c\uc0\u361 ng... y\'eau c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  Di\'ean b\u7843 o b\u7889 i trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  l\'fac khai gi\u7843 ng nghi\'ean c\u7913 u sinh l\u226 \u768 n \u273 \u226 \u768 u ti\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec sao, t\'f4i l\u7841 i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7897 t y\'eau v\u7853 t...\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7899  m\'e3i kh\'f4ng qu\'ean, nh\u7845 t ki\u7871 n chung t\'ecnh.\cb1 \
