\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tho\uc0\u7841 t \u273 \u7847 u l\'fac c\u7843 m gi\'e1c Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7921 a t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tin, sau \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n c\u7913  t\u7921  nhi\'ean nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\u7915 ng th\u7847 m y\'ean l\u7863 ng \u273 \'f3n nh\u7853 n, v\u7915 a \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i v\u7915 a gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng t\u7921  m\'ecnh ch\'e0o h\'e0ng: "Y\'ean t\'e2m, A Di\'ean, ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u7903  c\u7841 nh t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ra t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e2u, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7921  ti. T\'f4i cam \u273 oan s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  d\u7845 u v\u7871 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t ai kh\'e1c ngo\'e0i c\u7853 u. M\'e0 c\'f3 b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao, b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e1nh kh\'f4ng l\u7841 i t\'f4i... N\u7871 u c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng tin t\'f4i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u432 \u417 ng t\u7893 n c\u7853 u, t\'f4i s\u7869  ch\u7913 ng minh cho c\u7853 u xem, m\u7897 t ng\'e0y, hai ng\'e0y, ba ng\'e0y, ch\u7913 ng minh c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 ai b\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i cho n\'ean \u7903  c\'f9ng c\u7853 u s\u7869  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7921  ti \u273 \'e2u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \'f4n nhu nh\u432  v\u7853 y \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ch\'e2n nh\u361 n ra, nghe Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai m\'ecnh li\'ean mi\'ean l\u7843 i nh\u7843 i n\'f3i nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i bu\u7891 n n\'f4n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng dinh d\u432 \u7905 ng n\'e0y, l\u7841 i c\'e0ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7911 ng n\u7883 ch \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c h\u417 i n\'f3ng l\'ean: "H\u7915 , c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch v\'ec sao n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i \u7913 c hi\u7871 p t\'f4i \u273 i, \u7913 c hi\u7871 p t\'f4i th\'ec th\'f4i, ngay c\u7843  m\u7863 t m\u361 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7897 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u nh\u432  n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng s\u7907  th\'e0nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432  t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, t\'f4i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh trong c\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec sao, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y bu\u7891 n b\u7921 c hay t\u7883 ch m\u7883 ch, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t tr\u7889 ng. Sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y t\'f4i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u, l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y, c\'f3 l\u7869  cho t\u7899 i b\'e2y gi\u7901 , t\'f4i ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 ang \u273 \u7907 i c\u7853 u, ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 ang t\'ecm c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'ec v\uc0\u7853 y t\'f4i li\u7873 n thu\u7853 n theo l\'f2ng m\'ecnh \u273 i t\'ecm c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng sau m\u7845 y \u273 \'eam \'f4m c\u7853 u \u273 \'f3, nguy\'ean b\u7843 n c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng t\u7883 ch m\u7883 ch \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tr\u7903  n\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng n\u7893 i. T\'f4i g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng k\'ecm n\'e9n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c mu\u7889 n \u273 u\u7893 i theo c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i lo l\u7855 ng d\u7885 a c\u7853 u s\u7907  n\'ean m\u7899 i mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng nh\u7883 n xu\u7889 ng. V\u7853 y n\'ean v\u7873  sau \u7903  trong tr\'f2 ch\u417 i ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n c\u7853 u, bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7889  \'fd mu\u7889 n g\u7841 t c\u7853 u, ch\u7881  l\'e0 s\u7907  c\u7853 u l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3, b\u7883  t\'f4i \'f4m m\u7897 t c\'e1i li\u7873 n s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c kh\'f3c ng\u7845 t \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \'edch x\'e1c l\'e0 t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i m\u7845 t m\u7863 t "Kh\'f3c ng\u7845 t \u273 i", nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n c\u7853 u l\'e0m ch\u7881  l\'e0 "\'d4m m\u7897 t c\'e1i" th\'f4i \'e0? Song h\'e0m ngh\u297 a \u7849 n trong l\u7901 i n\'f3i c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng qu\'e1 m\u7913 c ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\'e2m t\u432  t\u7915 ng ch\'fat bay l\'ean, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng so \u273 o nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i g\uc0\u7885 i l\'e0 *qu\u7927  tho\u7841 i li\'ean thi\'ean y\'eau ng\'f4n ho\u7863 c ch\'fang, th\'ec ra Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i l\u7901 i y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m cho m\'ecnh ngay c\u7843  t\'e2m c\u361 ng b\u7883  m\'ea ho\u7863 c.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (qu\uc0\u7927  tho\u7841 i li\'ean thi\'ean y\'eau ng\'f4n ho\u7863 c ch\'fang : l\u7901 i b\u7883 a \u273 \u7863 t m\'ea ho\u7863 c ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c kia th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 \u7873 u lu\'f4n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3 c\'f4 \uc0\u273 \u417 n kh\'f4ng?" C\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 au l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng, t\'f4i v\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i r\u7891 i, tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac g\u7863 p c\u7853 u, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u c\'e1i g\'ec g\u7885 i l\'e0 c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n, c\'e1i g\'ec g\u7885 i l\'e0 t\u7883 ch m\u7883 ch l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\uc0\u7841 m quy, gi\u7901  l\u7841 i c\'e0ng \u273 au l\'f2ng h\u417 n r\u7891 i. Tuy r\u7857 ng bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, tuy r\u7857 ng b\u7843 n n\u259 ng mang suy ngh\u297  "Kh\'f4ng c\'f9ng gi\u7889 ng lo\'e0i v\u7899 i m\'ecnh t\'e2m nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'e1c" r\u7891 i \'f4m c\u7843 m gi\'e1c s\u7907  h\'e3i kh\'f4ng r\'f5 \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i y\'eau v\u7853 t, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng trong \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hi\u7879 n l\'ean h\'ecnh \u7843 nh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  nh\'e0 b\u7853 n r\u7897 n l\'e0m l\u7849 u\'97\'97trong nh\u7919 ng n\u259 m th\'e1ng d\'e0i \u273 \u7857 ng \u273 \u7861 ng khi b\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u432 a xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng l\'e0m l\u7849 u \u432 ? \u258 n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u432 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'fac nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i n\'f3i kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i, ch\u7881  nghe Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7843 n nhi\'ean n\'f3i: "Cho n\'ean m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u \u273 i, l\u7847 n n\'e0y n\u7871 u c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n r\u7901 i \u273 i, v\u7873  sau th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, t\'f4i ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "N\uc0\u7871 u t\'f4i ch\u7871 t th\'ec sao?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\u7913 c h\u7887 i ra l\u7901 i, trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t ghi ch\'e9p l\u7841 i, y\'eau v\u7853 t \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 m\u7841 ng s\u7889 ng d\'e0i l\'e2u, m\'e0 con ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7881  c\'f9ng l\u7855 m l\'e0 tr\u259 m n\u259 m gi\'e2y l\'e1t, kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u gi\u432 \u417 ng m\u7855 t, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y th\u7847 n s\u7855 c nghi\'eam t\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c gi\u7901  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f3 c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f9ng nhau ch\uc0\u7871 t. C\u7853 u ch\u7871 t t\'f4i s\u7869  c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ch\u7871 t, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t t\'f4i s\u7869  c\'f9ng c\u7853 u bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, c\u7853 u lu\'e2n h\u7891 i, t\'f4i s\u7869  theo c\u7853 u chuy\u7875 n th\u7871 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau l\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  qu\u7929  \u273 \u7841 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn ra quan h\u7879  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i v\u7899 i \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e3o Vi\'ean quan h\u7879  th\'e2n thi\u7871 t nh\u7845 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean \u273 \'e3 th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n n\'f3i th\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean r\uc0\u7845 t kinh ng\u7841 c: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867  \'e0, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\u7853 u c\'f3 khuynh h\u432 \u7899 ng ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 nha, sao l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u7903  b\'ean ti\u7875 u t\u7917  kia?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ho khan m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "\u7914  th\'ec, ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u7903  chung l\'e2u n\'ean c\'f3 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean d\'f9ng \'e1nh m\uc0\u7855 t kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u m\u7899 i \u7903  chung v\u7899 i h\u7855 n m\u7897 t h\u7885 c k\'ec, \u7903  v\u7899 i t\'f4i th\u7871  nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7889 n n\u259 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "... K\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t l\u226 \u768 n \u273 \u226 \u768 u ti\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y h\u7855 n t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t c\'f3 h\u7843 o c\u7843 m, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t th\'e2n thi\u7871 t, r\u7845 t quen thu\u7897 c, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y h\u7855 n s\u7869  r\u7845 t vui v\u7867 . V\u7873  sau t\'f4i g\u7863 p ch\'fat kh\'f3 kh\u259 n, h\u7855 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  t\'f4i, t\'f4i li\u7873 n c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng c\'f3 c\u7843 m t\'ecnh v\u7899 i h\u7855 n. Sau \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n h\u7855 n c\'f3 ch\'fat khuy\u7871 t \u273 i\u7875 m, h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f2n t\u7915 ng g\u7841 t t\'f4i, nh\u432 ng l\'fac \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t th\'edch h\u7855 n, cho n\'ean tuy r\u7857 ng l\'fac m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t s\u7907 , s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  suy ngh\u297 , ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n t\u7853 n l\u7921 c tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i h\u7855 n, c\u361 ng kh\'e1ng c\u7921  m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian... Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o ch\u7889 ng l\u7841 i t\'e2m \'fd c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7855 n. May m\'e0 h\u7855 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean t\'f4i, kh\'f4ng cho t\'f4i kh\'f4ng gian c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean b\uc0\u7845 y gi\u7901  b\u7845 t ng\u7901  kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng b\u7883  *c\u7849 u l\u432 \u417 ng ng\u7853 p m\u7891 m. H\u7855 n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng t\'e2m s\u7921  r\u7889 i r\u7855 m t\u7921 a thi\u7871 u n\u7919  kia c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\u7913 ng th\'fa, ch\u7881  b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai t\u7915  m\u7845 u ch\u7889 t ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a: "C\'e1i g\'ec? ! C\'f3 khuy\u7871 t \u273 i\u7875 m, c\'f2n t\u7915 ng l\u7915 a g\u7841 t c\u7853 u?"\cb1 \

