\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Khuy\uc0\u7871 t \u273 i\u7875 m c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  b\u7841 n m\'ecnh \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i, c\'f2n d\'f9ng ng\u7919  kh\'ed n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  n\'f3i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  nh\u7887 , l\'e3o Vi\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c: "Khuy\u7871 t \u273 i\u7875 m g\'ec? T\u7915 ng ph\u7841 m t\u7897 i? Hay t\u7915 ng h\'fat ma t\'fay?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng, Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\u7879  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\u7855 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'e1nh n\uc0\u7863 ng t\'ecm nh\u7865  \u273 \'e1p: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3, ch\'ednh l\'e0 h\u7855 n k\u7923  th\u7853 t \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\'f4i, nh\'e0 h\u7855 n c\'e1ch nh\'e0 ch\'fa t\'f4i t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i g\u7847 n, th\u7871  n\'ean l\'fac t\'f4i t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p trung h\u7885 c \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ch\'fa \u7903 , m\u7895 i \u273 \'eam h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883 t m\u7863 t leo qua ban c\'f4ng l\u7867 n v\'e0o ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u7911 a t\'f4i l\'e0m t\'f4i s\u7907 . Sau n\'e0y l\'fac g\u7863 p l\u7841 i h\u7855 n c\'f2n nghi\'eam trang \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7855 n gi\u7843  b\u7897  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3, h\u7895 n \u273 \u7843 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7921  nh\u7853 n vi\u7879 c n\'e0y m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t ph\'fac h\u7853 u r\u7891 i , c\u7853 u \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 th\u7875  x\u432 ng l\'e0 h\u7871 t l\'f2ng quan t\'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean tr\uc0\u7907 n m\u7855 t h\'e1 m\u7891 m s\u7901  c\u7857 m: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7913 ? B\u7841 n c\u7853 u tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn \u432 u nh\'e3 \u273 \'fang m\u7921 c \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m ra lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t lu\u7853 n l\'e0 b\u7883 t m\u7863 t leo ban c\'f4ng chui v\'e0o ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta hay l\'e0 gi\u7889 ng h\u7885 c sinh ti\u7875 u h\u7885 c ng\'e2y th\u417  chuy\'ean d\u7885 a n\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh th\'edch, \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng chuy\u7879 n v\u7883  kia c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nha.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a nh\'ecn \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y gi\u7889 ng c\'f4ng t\u7917  quy\u7873 n qu\'fd l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng c\u7845 m d\u7909 c nh\u432  h\u7855 n, n\u7871 u th\'edch ai \u273 \'f3 th\'ec ch\u7859 ng ph\u7843 i n\'ean l\'e0 ki\u7875 u th\u7853 n tr\u7885 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean t\u7863 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ta b\u7843 y, t\'e1m c\'e1i nh\'e0, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i t\u7887  v\u7867  t\'f4i t\u7863 ng nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd t\u7913  g\'ec kh\'e1c m\'e0 ch\u7881  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n k\u7871 t b\u7841 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u th\'f4i sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, l\'e3o Vi\'ean nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n n\'f3i: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , v\u7883  kia nh\'e0 c\u7853 u nh\'ecn qua b\u7889 i c\u7843 nh r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia \u273 \'e3 t\u7863 ng c\u7853 u c\'e1i nh\'e0 n\'e0o ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3. Nh\'e0 b\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  h\u7855 n \u7903  c\u361 ng l\'e0 \u273 i m\u432 \u7907 n. A, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u h\u7855 n d\u7885 a ch\u7911  nh\'e0 ch\u7841 y, ch\u7911  nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o n\'ean \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i \u273 em nh\'e0 cho h\u7855 n m\u432 \u7907 n \u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn l\'e3o Vi\'ean khinh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng: "... \'cdt xem ng\'f4n t\'ecnh \u273 i, t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7913  \u273 \u7885 c nhi\u7873 u ng\'f4n t\'ecnh l\'e0 c\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'e2m l\'fd con g\'e1i r\u7891 i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7841 n g\'e1i \u273 \'e2u." \u272 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 b\u7841 n g\'e1i kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n t\u432  duy c\u7911 a m\'ecnh b\u7883  ch\u7881 nh th\'e0nh si\'eau th\u7921 c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 ang c\'f3 d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean r\uc0\u7845 t oan \u7913 c, r\u7847 m r\'ec r\u7847 m r\'ec kh\'f4ng n\'f3i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7847 n d\u7847 n ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7889 ng cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  r\u7845 t \u259 n \'fd, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 \u7903  chung, ma s\'e1t c\u7921 c k\u7923  l\'e2u r\u7891 i. Ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n nhi\u7873 u l\u7901 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u \'fd c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang nh\u432  l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra h\u7855 n r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec. Sau khi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p b\u7885 n h\u7885  th\'f4ng b\'e1o k\u7871 t h\'f4n, ng\u432 \u7901 i xung quanh c\'f9ng l\u7855 m l\'e0 s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t chuy\u7879 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 nam gi\u7899 i, th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t chuy\u7879 n m\u7897 t trong hai ch\'fa r\u7875  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'e2m th\u7847 m c\u7843 m kh\'e1i con ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u thi\u7875 n c\u7853 n nh\u432  th\u7871 , v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ai xuy\'ean qua hi\u7879 n t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7843 n ch\u7845 t, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i t\u7921  nhi\'ean sinh ra m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u say m\'ecnh ta t\u7881 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7871 ch l\'f4ng m\'e0y n\'f3i: "N\'e0y th\'ec c\'f3 g\'ec hay m\'e0 \u273 \u7855 c \'fd? C\'f2n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec t\'f4i ch\u7881  t\u7889 t v\u7899 i m\'ecnh c\u7853 u \u432 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ti\uc0\u7871 p l\u7901 i, nh\u432 ng trong b\u7909 ng l\u7841 i t\u7921  nhi\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'e0ng th\'eam \u273 \u7855 c \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i l\'e0 c\'e0ng \u7903  b\'ean nhau c\'e0ng l\'e2u, b\u7843 n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\'e0ng lo l\u7855 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  b\u7883  cao nh\'e2n ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 i. B\u7903 i v\'ec chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a C\u7889  T\'edch T\'edch, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 H\u7891  Tinh Ti\u7875 u An c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  th\'e0nh b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u, khi n\'e0o b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A l\'e0m vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  g\u7863 p m\u7863 t t\u7909  h\u7885 p v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7843 o m\u7855 t l\u7841 i n\u259 m n\u259 m tr\'f4i qua, l\u7847 n n\'e0y H\u7891  Tinh l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  A h\u7895  tr\u7907  xem x\'e9t m\u7897 t v\u7909  \'e1n, sau khi c\'f4ng t\'e1c k\u7871 t th\'fac li\u7873 n h\u7865 n l\'e3o Vi\'ean v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i \u259 n c\u417 m, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t nh\u7855 n r\'f5 d\u7851 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi theo.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin nh\u7855 n r\u7845 t do d\u7921 , lo l\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng y\'ean nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau: "Hay l\'e0 c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng, t\'f4i ph\uc0\u7843 i \u273 i, H\u7891  Tinh gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u cho c\u7853 u y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i kh\'e1c th\'ec sao? Ng\u7897  nh\u7905  c\u7853 u b\u7883  y\'eau qu\'e1i kh\'e1c c\'e2u d\u7851 n ch\u7841 y m\u7845 t th\'ec sao? Ch\u7859 ng ph\u7843 i t\'f4i s\u7869  r\u7845 t \u273 au kh\u7893  \u432 ?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 l\u7845 y XONG qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\'e0 ph\u7909  ki\u7879 n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i cho hai ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\uc0\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i \u273 ang n\'f3i lung tung, H\u7891  Tinh sao c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i cho m\'ecnh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c? D\u7913 t kho\'e1t kh\'f4ng th\'e8m \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\u7899 i h\u7855 n, ch\u7881  n\'f3i ra lo l\u7855 ng c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n: "T\'f4i nghe n\'f3i hai n\u259 m qua H\u7891  Tinh c\'f4ng l\u7921 c t\u259 ng m\u7841 nh, c\u7853 u b\u7883  nh\'ecn ra th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7915  ph\'eda sau \'f4m l\u7845 y c\u7853 u, c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c h\'edp m\u7855 t l\u7841 i: "N\u432 \u417 ng t\u7917  lo l\u7855 ng cho ta \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e0 lo l\uc0\u7855 ng t\'f4i *th\u7911  ho\u7841 t qu\u7843 ." Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7841  m\u7855 t thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7855 n m\'e0 \u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i, ng\u7849 n ng\u417  nh\u7899  l\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 l\u7901 i n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i b\u7883  c\'e2u n\'e0y l\u7845 y l\'f2ng, c\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i l\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7853 u: "T\'f4i bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u luy\u7871 n ti\u7871 c t\'f4i nh\u7845 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'f2ng v\u7851 n run s\u7907  m\'e0 d\u7855 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i. C\u7853 u ngh\u297  l\'e3o Di\u7879 p ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n \'e1c, H\u7891  Tinh l\u7841 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i quen bi\u7871 t, b\u7873  ngo\'e0i kh\'f4n kh\'e9o l\'e3o luy\u7879 n b\'ean trong k\u7923  th\u7853 t m\u7873 m m\u7841 i v\'f4 c\'f9ng. B\u7883  ch\u7883  nh\'ecn ra chung quy t\u7889 t h\u417 n so v\u7899 i m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 v\'f4 \'fd b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c nh\'ecn ra, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  xin ch\u7883  gi\'fap ngh\u297  bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p che gi\u7845 u thay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i m\u7885 i th\u7913  nh\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i sau khi nh\'ecnTr\'ec Di\'ean k\u7929  l\u432 \u7905 ng h\u7891 i l\'e2u, nh\'edu m\'e0y n\'f3i: "C\'e1i c\u7853 u n\'e0y l\'e0m g\'ec th\u7871 ? Sao m\u7895 i l\u7847 n g\u7863 p c\u7853 u t\'e0 kh\'ed tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u d\'e0y h\u417 n l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i n\'e0y th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 n\'f3i kh\'f4ng th\'f4ng, xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p n\'e0y b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai nguy\'ean nh\'e2n: M\u7897 t l\'e0 ng\'e0y ng\'e0y s\u7889 ng \u7903  n\u417 i t\'e0 kh\'ed c\u7921 c n\u7863 ng, nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7871 u qu\u7843  th\u7853 t quanh n\u259 m s\u7889 ng trong ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh \u273 \'f3 s\u7907  l\'e0 s\u7869  b\u7879 nh t\u7853 t qu\u7845 n th\'e2n ho\u7863 c \u273 o\u7843 n m\u7879 nh m\'e0 ch\u7871 t; hai l\'e0 c\u7843  ng\'e0y l\'e0m b\u7841 n v\u7899 i y\'eau t\'e0, ti\u7871 p x\'fac th\'e2n m\u7853 t, c\'e1i n\'e0y \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng c\'f3 h\u7841 i. Nh\u432 ng nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7883  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i, kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  n\'e0o t\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \u7841 i t\'e0, b\u7841 n b\'e8 th\'e2n thi\u7871 t b\'ean c\u7841 nh th\u432 \u7901 ng qua l\u7841 i ch\u7883  \'edt nhi\u7873 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 ch\'fat \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai l\'e0 y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c bi\u7871 t vi\u7879 c n\'e0y tho\'e1t kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i li\'ean quan v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, nh\u432 ng qua loa n\'f3i: "H\u7891  t\u7927  ch\u7883  l\'e0 chuy\'ean gia c\'f2n kh\'f4ng r\'f5, em l\'e0m sao bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. V\'f4 h\u7841 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng t\'e0 kh\'ed n\'e0y c\u361 ng x\'e1c th\u7921 c k\'ec l\u7841  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng h\u7873  t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng th\'e2n th\u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean, H\u7891  Tinh ngh\u297  kh\'f4ng ra nguy\'ean nh\'e2n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u tr\u7901 i cao bi\u7875 n r\u7897 ng kh\'f4ng thi\u7871 u s\u7921  l\u7841 , ch\u7883  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  quy cho b\u7843 n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean thi\'ean ph\'fa d\u7883  b\u7849 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7863 ng l\u7869  gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng th\u7887 a m\'e3n n\'f3i: "Tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i, t\'f4i l\u432 u l\u7841 i tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
