\cf2 \cb3 Ai ch\uc0\u7843  bi\u7871 t l\'e0 c\u7853 u l\'e0m, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u sao c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i d\'f9ng ng\u7919  kh\'ed nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u7875  n\'f3i? ! Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7853 n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ph\'e1t ti\u7871 t v\u7863 n ch\u7863 t c\u7893  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7855 n l\'ean c\u7893  h\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh ho khan m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn l\u7841 i, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'e0n ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 ang nh\'ecn m\'ecnh v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 \uc0\u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 thi\u7871 u ni\'ean tu\u7893 i tr\u7867  da m\u7863 t m\u7887 ng, nh\u432 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 b\u7841 n b\'e8 quen bi\u7871 t, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7841 i sao \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \'e1p Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i lu\'f4n d\u7877  d\'e0ng \u273 \'e1nh m\u7845 t l\'fd tr\'ed nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Qu\u7843  nhi\'ean l\'e0 h\u7891 ng nhan h\u7885 a th\u7911 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891  Tinh v\u7851 n \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean th\'e2n thi\u7879 n c\u432 \u7901 i an \u7911 i c\u7853 u: "Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec, kh\'f4ng sao \u273 \'e2u, m\u7845 y n\u259 m nay b\u7885 n t\'f4i c\u361 ng quen r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y an \u7911 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i ti\u7871 p: "Nh\'ecn xem, A Di\'ean, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u lu\'f4n \u7913 c hi\u7871 p t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o Vi\'ean ph\uc0\u7843 n \u7913 ng ch\u7853 m m\u7897 t nh\u7883 p, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p n\'f3i ti\u7871 p: "Kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang nha, Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867  t\u7915 ng k\u7875  cho t\'f4i chuy\u7879 n n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 l\'fac c\u7853 u ta ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u th\u7915 a d\u7883 p tr\u7901 i t\u7889 i b\u7883 t m\u7863 t leo ban c\'f4ng chui v\'e0o ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u ta h\'f9 d\u7885 a c\u7853 u ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7875 u An nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7845 t ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7913 ? Di\u7879 p ca c\u361 ng l\'e0m lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n l\'e3o Vi\'ean \u273 ang n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n, tr\'ean m\u7863 t hi\u7879 n l\'ean n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  x\u432 ng l\'e0 d\u7883 u d\'e0ng h\u7841 nh ph\'fac: "\u7914 , m\u7863 c d\'f9 h\u417 i c\'f3 l\u7895 i v\u7899 i A Di\'ean, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 b\'e2y gi\u7901  nh\u7899  l\u7841 i, \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng k\u7881  ni\u7879 m vui s\u432 \u7899 ng nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a t\'f4i, vui v\u7867  h\u417 n n\u7919 a ch\'ednh l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c A Di\'ean."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\uc0\u7871 t r\'f5 n\u7897 i t\'ecnh, nghe th\u7845 y h\u7855 n da m\u7863 t d\'e0y l\'ean ti\u7871 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  qu\u7843  th\u7921 c t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n \u273 \u7871 n mu\u7889 n c\u7855 n h\u7855 n, nh\u432 ng quay m\u7863 t sang l\u7841 i tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i \'f4n nhu nh\'ecn m\'ecnh, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en th\u7853 t s\'e2u, t\u7921 a nh\u432  l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u g\u7863 p g\u7905 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Khai gi\uc0\u7843 ng nghi\'ean c\u7913 u sinh ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u th\u7903  h\u7891 ng h\u7897 c x\'e1ch vali \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng k\'ed t\'fac ra, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\'ean trong \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang quay l\u432 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  nghe th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i, nhanh ch\'f3ng gi\'fap c\u7853 u thu d\u7885 n h\'e0nh l\'ed, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u432 a m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c kh\u259 n m\u7863 t qua, m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "T\'f4i l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi." Con ng\u432 \u417 i m\'e0u \u273 en ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, s\'e2u kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e1y.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 b\uc0\u7897  d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841  ch\u7899  g\u7847 n, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i \'f4n nhu ngo\'e0i \'fd mu\u7889 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\u297 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, th\u7853 t l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e1i t\'ean d\u7877  nghe, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c l\'e0 c\'e1i t\'ean \'eam tai nh\u7845 t c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  ngh\u297  ra.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 m ph\u7851 n tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p l\u7853 p t\u7913 c h\'f3a th\'e0nh m\u7897 t b\u7909 ng nhu t\'ecnh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  n\u7893 i c\u361 ng nh\'ecn h\u7855 n cong kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng. Th\'ec ra, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 \u7903  b\'ean nhau nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i h\u7855 n s\u7869  ch\u7913 ng minh h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng m\'ecnh. B\'e2y gi\u7901  chuy\u7879 n ch\u7913 ng minh n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  h\u7855 n l\'e0m c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i, \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 v\'ec kh\'f4ng tin hay s\u7907  h\'e3i, m\'e0 b\u7903 i c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7873  nh\'e0, tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac ng\u7911  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7901  l\'ean d\u7845 u r\u259 ng tr\'ean c\u7893  nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng o\'e1n th\'e1n n\'f3i: "T\u7915  khi n\'e0o l\u7841 i th\'eam th\'f3i quen th\'edch c\u7855 n ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i, t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n c\u361 ng c\u7855 n, vui v\u7867  c\u361 ng c\u7855 n." D\u7845 u r\u259 ng n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i d\u7845 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7865 n qu\'e1 ho\'e1 gi\u7853 n c\u7855 n \u7903  nh\'e0 h\'e0ng tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 m\'e0 l\'e0 do c\u7853 u v\u7915 a m\u7899 i c\u7855 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\'fac n\'e0o c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\u7855 n t\'f4i, c\'f3 v\u7867  *phu c\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a t\'f4i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, t\'f4i ph\u7843 i tr\u7843  th\'f9."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (phu c\uc0\u432 \u417 ng: uy th\u7871  l\'e0m ch\u7891 ng)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7879 t m\u7887 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra \'e2m u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7853 p t\u7913 c s\u7917 a mi\u7879 ng: "Ki\u7871 p sau tr\u7843 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y d\u7845 u r\u259 ng tr\'ean c\u7893  h\u7855 n, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c h\u417 i x\u7845 u h\u7893 : "... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u mau x\'f3a c\'e1i d\u7845 u \u273 \'f3 \u273 i, ng\'e0y mai \u273 i l\'e0m b\u7883  \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi lo\u7841 i y\'eau t\'e0 n\'e0y, to\'e0n b\u7897  th\u7921 c th\u7875  \u273 \u7873 u t\u7921  m\'ecnh ng\u432 ng k\u7871 t m\'e0 th\'e0nh, x\'f3a m\u7897 t v\u7871 t c\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nghe, \u273 \u7855 c \'fd vu\u7889 t v\u7871 t c\u7855 n nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i ng\u7911 : "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng th\'edch, t\'f4i ph\u7843 i l\u432 u n\'f3 l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7855 n h\u7855 n th\'ec h\u7855 n o\'e1n th\'e1n, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\'f3 d\u7845 u r\u259 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  th\'ec ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i l\u7841 i vui v\u7867 , xem nh\u432  b\u7843 o b\u7889 i che l\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u ti\'eau tr\u7915  \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7849 y h\u7855 n hai c\'e1i, h\u7855 n l\u7841 i gi\u7843  b\u7897  nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 ng\u7911 , kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i h\'e0nh vi v\'f4 l\u7841 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i y\'ean l\u7863 ng k\'e9o ch\u259 n ng\u7911 . L\'fac n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i l\u7841 i c\'f3 \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c, v\u432 \u417 n tay k\'e9o ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi t\uc0\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p ba n\u259 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi chung nhau mua nh\'e0 c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, chuy\u7875 n kh\u7887 i c\u259 n nh\'e0 "\u7902  nh\u7901 " n\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i t\'ecnh nh\'e2n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7845 t tr\'ean th\u7871  gian n\'e0y, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y g\u7885 i nhau th\u7913 c gi\u7845 c, t\'ecm qu\u7847 n \'e1o cho nhau, th\u7855 t c\'e0 v\u7841 t, t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 i l\'e0m, sau m\u7897 t ng\'e0y b\u7853 n r\u7897 n l\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\'e0, \u259 n c\u417 m, t\u7855 m r\u7917 a, \u273 i ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng s\u7869  t\u7853 n l\u7921 c m\'e0 s\u7855 p x\u7871 p th\u7901 i gian ngh\u7881  ph\'e9p h\u7857 ng n\u259 m tr\'f9ng nhau, t\'ecm m\u7897 t n\u417 i \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng ho\u7863 c ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng t\u7899 i \u273 \u7875  \u273 i du l\u7883 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mu\u7889 n, h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7921 a v\'e0o n\u259 ng l\u7921 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh d\u7877  d\'e0ng \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng tha thi\u7871 t m\u417  \u432 \u7899 c, nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n t\'ecnh nguy\u7879 n ng\u7909 y trang b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'e0nh m\u7897 t con ng\u432 \u7901 i tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'ec cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a c\u7843  hai d\u7889 c s\u7913 c l\'e0m vi\u7879 c, c\'f9ng nhau tr\u7843  ti\u7873 n nh\'e0, c\'f9ng nhau chia s\u7867  m\u7897 t c\u7889 c h\u7891 ng tr\'e0 n\'f3ng trong \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f4ng. M\u7895 i th\u7913  h\u7855 n cho ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 do t\u7921  tay h\u7855 n t\u7915 ng ch\'fat m\u7897 t ki\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i gian th\u7853 t d\'e0i l\'e2u, \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng s\u7869  qu\'ean s\u7921  th\u7853 t ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau m\'ecnh th\u7853 t ra kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, d\'f9 c\'f3 nh\u7899  ra c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\u7853 n m\u7855 t nh\'ecn th\u7845 y s\u7907 i t\'f3c tr\u7855 ng \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kinh ng\u7841 c b\u7855 t l\u7845 y n\'f3i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, anh c\u361 ng s\u7869  gi\'e0 \u273 i sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u417 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u nh\u7893  t\'f3c, t\'f9y \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean. \u272 \u7915 ng tin m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n th\u7847 n tho\u7841 i kia, c\'e1i g\'ec kh\'f4ng gi\'e0 kh\'f4ng ch\u7871 t \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 b\u7883 a ra g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7845 y, \u273 i ng\u432 \u7907 c v\u7899 i quy lu\u7853 t khoa h\u7885 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t may ba ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c h\u7855 n ng\u7911  d\u7853 y tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7885 c m\u7897 t s\u7907 i, b\'e8n th\u7915 a d\u7883 p ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\'f2n \u273 ang ch\'ecm trong gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng l\'e9n nh\u7893  n\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7875 , t\'f4i mu\u7889 n gi\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c em m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\u432  v\u7853 y em v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n l\'e0 ti\u7875 u b\u7843 o b\u7889 i c\u7911 a t\'f4i, v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n c\'f3 th\u7875  h\u7891  \u273 \u7891  \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t t\'f4i, t\'f9y h\u7913 ng, l\'e0m n\u361 ng v\u7899 i t\'f4i, th\u7887 a th\'edch l\'e0m b\u7853 y. Y\'eau t\'e0 kh\'f4ng gi\'e0 kh\'f4ng ch\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng t\'f4i s\u7869  c\'f9ng em gi\'e0 \u273 i, c\'f9ng em \u273 i h\u7871 t m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng t\'f4i c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u em m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 quen, ki\u7871 p sau em l\u7841 i b\u7883  y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i kh\'e1c hay k\u7867  n\'e0o kh\'e1c c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 i, ch\u7859 ng ph\u7843 i t\'f4i s\u7869  r\u7845 t thi\u7879 t hay sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n d\u7851 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i mua th\u7913 c \u259 n nh\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng ng\'e0y, c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i, v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra mi\u7879 ng v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau. T\u7921 a nh\u432  y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng \u7849 n s\'e2u n\u417 i \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng, kh\'f4ng b\u7887  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\u7845 y ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  s\u7921  bi\u7871 n \u273 \u7893 i kh\'f4n l\u432 \u7901 ng, n\u259 m th\'e1ng nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng tr\'f4i, nh\'e2n gian v\'e0i th\u7853 p ni\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn l\u7841 i c\u361 ng ch\u7881  trong ch\u7899 p m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7847 n d\u7847 n l\'fac v\u7873  gi\'e0 th\'edch y\'ean l\u7863 ng n\u7855 m tay ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u7903  nh\'e0 \u273 eo k\'ednh l\'e3o ng\u7891 i \u7903  b\'e0n th\u7911 y tinh tr\'ean s\'e2n th\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7885 c s\'e1ch, gi\'e0 r\u7891 i r\u7845 t kh\'f3 t\u7853 p trung l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd, chung quy s\u7869  lu\'f4n th\u7845 t th\u7847 n m\'e0 ngh\u297 , c\'f3 th\u7875  g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7853 t t\u7889 t, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7869  y\'eau m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, c\'f3 l\u7869  ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f4 \u273 \u7897 c qua m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian v\u7873  sau, c\u7853 u m\u7899 i ng\u7891 i tr\'ean s\'e2n th\u432 \u7907 ng m\u7897 t l\'e1t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  k\'e9o c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng, k\'eau c\u7853 u ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ph\'e1t gi\'e1c tr\u432 \u7899 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7889  ki\u7871 p c\u7911 a c\u7853 u s\u7855 p \u273 \u7871 n. Trong l\'f2ng h\u7855 n ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u bi th\u432 \u417 ng, d\'f9 sao b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n sau khi ch\u7871 t r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, h\u7855 n v\'e0 c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  b\'ean nhau.\cb1 \
