\cb3 Tr\'f2 chuy\uc0\u7879 n li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7901 i gian tr\'f4i qua nhanh h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u, r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n th\u7901 i gian l\'ean m\'e1y bay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean ng\u7891 i m\'e1y bay nh\u7887  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, m\u7895 i h\'e0ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 b\u7889 n ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i, m\u7895 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n x\'f3c n\u7843 y tr\'ean kh\'f4ng trung c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t th\'e0nh gh\u7871  nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ch\'f3ng m\u7863 t v\'e0 kh\'f4ng tr\u7885 ng l\u7921 c m\u7895 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n. Nh\u432 ng may m\'e0 th\u7901 i gian bay r\u7845 t ng\u7855 n, t\u7915  c\u7917 a s\u7893  tr\'f2n nh\'ecn ra b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y b\u7901  bi\u7875 n v\'e0 c\'e2y c\u7889 i xanh um t\u432 \u417 i t\u7889 t xa xa.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e1y bay c\uc0\u7845 t c\'e1nh, c\'f3 duy nh\u7845 t m\u7897 t n\u7919  ti\u7871 p vi\'ean t\'f3c v\'e0ng ph\u7909 c v\u7909  cho b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n nh\u7887  b\'e1nh m\'ec v\'e0 \u273 \u7891  u\u7889 ng, nh\'e2n vi\'ean ph\u7909 c v\u7909  thu d\u7885 n r\'e1c bo\u777 , m\'e1y bay s\u7855 p h\u7841  c\'e1nh \'97\'97 th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 h\'e0nh tr\'ecnh c\u7921 c nhanh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a m\u7899 i th\'edch \u7913 ng v\u7899 i x\'f3c n\u7843 y tr\'ean m\'e1y bay \u273 \'e3 ph\u7843 i chu\u7849 n b\u7883  xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\'e0o m\uc0\u7915 ng t\u7899 i Sophus." \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 c\'e2u n\'f3i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\'ean m\'e1y bay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a B\u7841 ch Thu c\'f3 \u273 \u432 a xe t\u7899 i s\'e2n bay \u273 \'f3n sinh vi\'ean, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 b\u7887  l\u7905  th\u7901 i gian tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c \u273 \u432 a xe t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  m\'ecnh g\u7885 i xe tr\u7903  v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e2n bay kh\'f4ng l\uc0\u7899 n, nh\u432 ng h\u7847 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ai, Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'e9o vali \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat m\u7899 i th\u7845 y m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 i nhanh m\u7845 y b\u432 \u7899 c ti\u7871 n l\'ean ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c: "Xin ch\'e0o, xin l\u7895 i, cho t\'f4i h\u7887 i n\'ean ch\u7901  taxi \u7903  \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean, h\u7855 n nh\'ecn qua t\u7847 m ba b\u7889 n m\u432 \u417 i tu\u7893 i, tr\'ean m\u7863 t d\'ednh v\u7871 t b\u7849 n, r\'e2u quai n\'f3n d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\'e2u kh\'f4ng c\u7841 o, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o ba l\u7895  m\'e0u \u273 en v\'e0 qu\u7847 n \u273 \'f9i c\'f9ng m\'e0u, ch\'e2n \u273 eo m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i x\u259 ng \u273 an \u273 en.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, mi\u7879 ng l\u7849 m b\u7849 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nghe hi\u7875 u h\u7855 n \u273 ang n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7853 u c\u361 ng nh\u7853 n ra b\u7843 n th\'e2n h\'ecnh nh\u432  h\u7887 i sai ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u, t\u7915  g\'f3c \u273 \u7897  n\'e0y v\u7915 a v\u7863 n c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\u7843 ng hi\u7879 u m\'e0u xanh lam \u273 \'e1nh d\u7845 u nh\u7853 n d\u7841 ng xe taxi.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Xin l\uc0\u7895 i \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m phi\u7873 n." C\u7853 u v\u7897 i v\'e0ng n\'f3i xong k\'e9o vali quay tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 i\u7875 m ch\u7901  taxi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng kia nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\u432 ng c\u7853 u, v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng l\u7849 m b\u7849 m:\cb1 \
\cb3 "... C\uc0\u7849 n th\u7853 n nanh vu\u7889 t trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i, x\'e9 r\'e1ch ng\u432 \u417 i, c\u7855 n \u273 \u7913 t ng\u432 \u417 i, u\u7889 ng m\'e1u ng\u432 \u417 i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "... K\uc0\u7867  tha h\u432 \u417 ng ng\'e2y th\u417  ngu ng\u7889 c, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n b\u7887  m\u7841 ng \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y..."\cb1 \
