\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Xe taxi m\'e0u tr\uc0\u7855 ng ch\u7841 y nhanh tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n, trong xe ph\'e1t nh\u7841 c \u273 \u7891 ng qu\'ea tu\u7847 n ho\'e0n, m\u7903  c\u7917 a s\u7893  th\'ec c\'f3 gi\'f3 n\'f3ng ch\'e1y th\u7893 i \u273 \u7871 n, mang theo nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i th\'e1ng hai c\u7911 a b\'e1n c\u7847 u nam.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i h\u7847 u nh\u432  ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c khu d\'e2n c\u432  th\u7845 p nh\u7887  v\'e0 th\u7921 c v\u7853 t c\'e2y c\u7889 i b\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, t\u7915 ng d\u7843 i t\u7915 ng d\u7843 i phong c\u7843 nh l\'e0ng m\u7841 c ru\u7897 ng \u273 \u7891 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 n\u417 i k\u7871  c\u7853 n trung t\'e2m th\'e0nh ph\u7889  m\u7899 i c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'ed t\u7913 c hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7841 i ho\'e1. \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\u7889  tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0 xe \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t \'edt th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng taxi d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t t\'f2a nh\'e0 cao b\u7889 n n\u259 m t\u7847 ng. L\'e1i xe nh\u7853 n t\u7901  n\u259 m m\u432 \u417 i \u273 \'f4 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i, l\u7847 u b\u7847 u l\u7849 m b\u7849 m t\'ecm ti\u7873 n l\u7867  cho c\u7853 u: "Sau n\'e0y \u273 \u7915 ng c\u7847 m ti\u7873 n m\u7879 nh gi\'e1 l\u7899 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 i taxi, r\u7845 t kh\'f3 tr\u7843  l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean xu\uc0\u7889 ng xe, l\u432 ng \u273 eo ba l\'f4 x\'e1ch theo vali c\u7847 m m\u7897 t \'edt ti\u7873 n l\u7867  \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f2a k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 t\u432 \u417 ng lai c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, \u7903  trong n\u432 \u7899 c hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  ngay c\u7843  ti\u7873 n xu n\u259 m h\'e0o c\u361 ng r\u7845 t \'edt th\u7845 y, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \u273 \u7889 ng ti\u7873 n xu nh\u432  v\u7853 y khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u h\u417 i kh\'f4ng quen, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean \u273 \u7875  \u7903  \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u7897 t b\'ean c\u7845 t ti\u7873 n l\u7867 , m\u7897 t b\'ean quan s\'e1t t\'f2a nh\'e0 m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  s\u7853 m tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t. T\'f2a nh\'e0 n\'e0y h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 s\u417 n m\u7897 t v\'e0i n\u259 m, nh\'ecn t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\'f3 ch\'fat c\u361  k\u7929  khi\u7871 n cho m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  s\u7853 m kia tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn h\u417 i gi\u7889 ng v\u7871 t m\'e1u kh\'f4 sau khi l\u7855 ng \u273 \u7885 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u h\'edt m\u7897 t h\u417 i, k\'e9o vali \u273 i v\'e0o, c\u7917 a th\u7911 y tinh t\u7921  \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7903  sang hai b\'ean, b\'ean trong tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i m\u7899 i h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat so v\u7899 i b\u7873  ngo\'e0i, r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 tu s\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7853 n kh\'ed kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , l\'fac \u273 \u259 ng k\'fd xong c\u7847 m th\u7867  ph\'f2ng \u273 i l\'ean l\u7847 u li\u7873 n g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t nam sinh Trung Qu\u7889 c trong thang m\'e1y. Nam sinh t\'ean Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, t\u7899 i n\u417 i n\'e0y l\'e0 v\'ec tham gia m\u7897 t h\u7841 ng m\u7909 c "2+2" c\u7911 a tr\u432 \u7901 ng, h\u7841 ng m\u7909 c n\'e0y c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\'e0 \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c n\u259 m hai n\u259 m ba s\u7869  h\u7885 c \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i h\u7907 p t\'e1c v\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh, \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c n\u259 m b\u7889 n l\u7841 i quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng chu\u7849 n b\u7883  t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p ch\u7901  vi\u7879 c, cho n\'ean tuy r\u7857 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  h\u7855 n v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 h\u7885 c \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c n\u259 m ba nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y m\u7897 t n\u259 m, m\u7885 i ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t quen thu\u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u7903  l\u7847 u b\u7889 n, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u7903  l\u7847 u ba, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng gi\'fap Tr\'ec Di\'ean mang \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c l\'ean ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u, c\'f9ng c\u7853 u thu d\u7885 n ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "M\uc0\u7895 i l\u7847 u \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p chung, c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  n\u7845 u c\u417 m, c\'f2n c\'f3 ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m ph\'f2ng gi\u7863 t, qu\'e9t th\u7867  ph\'f2ng l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  v\'e0o; ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u n\'f3i th\u7853 t ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u v\u7883  tr\'ed kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t l\u7855 m \u273 \'e2u, l\u7847 u ph\'eda tr\'ean l\'e0 ph\'f2ng ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng, l\u7847 u n\u259 m l\'e0 kh\'f4ng gian chung, sinh vi\'ean n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i th\'edch m\u7903  party trong ph\'f2ng ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng, h\u7847 u nh\u432  m\u7895 i Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t \u273 \u7873 u m\u7903 , r\u7845 t \u7847 m \u297 . Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'e1c, c\u361 ng may b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901 . M\u7863 t kh\'e1c c\'f2n c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  mua \u273 \u7891  d\'f9ng sinh ho\u7841 t, \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng b\'e1o danh, l\'e0m v\'e9 xe bus, m\u7845 y vi\u7879 c \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'ecm t\'f4i, t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i, d\'f9 sao cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\'ednh th\u7913 c v\'e0o h\u7885 c, g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y r\u7845 t r\u7843 nh r\u7895 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7843 m \u417 n c\u7853 u." Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\u7901  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a h\u7887 i m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  b\u7843 n th\'e2n quan t\'e2m nh\u7845 t, "B\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u259 n c\u417 m nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o? \u258 n...\u273 \u7891  m\'ecnh t\u7921  l\'e0m sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "\u272 \'fang v\u7853 y, t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\'e0m."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\'ecn nh\'ecn v\u7867  m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Ho\u7863 c l\'e0 ra ngo\'e0i mua \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 r\u7867  nh\u7845 t c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i tr\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i m\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f4, h\u417 n n\u7919 a m\'f9i v\u7883  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, c\'f2n \u259 n kh\'f4ng ngon, kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng c\u417 m m\'ecnh l\'e0m v\u7915 a mi\u7879 ng. G\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y c\'f3 m\u7897 t ti\u7879 m hamburger nh\u7887 , c\'f3 b\'e1n hamburger, pizza, c\'e1 chi\'ean v\'e0 khoai t\'e2y, hamburger ph\u7847 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7887  ch\u7881  b\'e1n h\u417 n b\u7843 y \u273 \'f4. Pizza \u7903  ti\u7879 m \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'e1 ngon, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7897 t l\'ean men ph\u7911  th\u7883 t n\u432 \u7899 ng, c\'e0 r\u7889 t v\'e0 pho m\'e1t r\u7891 i n\u432 \u7899 ng th\'e0nh, ph\u7847 n nh\u7887  ch\u7881  b\'e1n t\u7847 m m\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f4, \u273 \u7911  \u259 n m\u7897 t ng\'e0y. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 d\u7847 u th\u7921 c v\u7853 t qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u nhi\u7879 t l\u432 \u7907 ng qu\'e1 l\u7899 n, \u259 n h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p n\u7845 u c\u417 m, v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 mua \u259 n th\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c c\u361 ng c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ch\u7895  b\'e1n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, nh\u432 ng m\'f9i v\u7883  s\u7889  l\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ngon l\u7855 m. Kh\'e1ch quan m\'e0 n\'f3i k\u7923  th\u7853 t t\'f4i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y subway r\u7845 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  t\'f4i v\u7851 n n\'ean t\u7921  h\u7885 c n\u7845 u th\'f4i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean bu\u7891 n r\u7847 u b\u432 ng \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u b\u7841 n m\u7899 i quen r\u7857 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n ngay c\u7843  b\u7871 p gas c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7853 t, l\'fac \u7903  nh\'e0 ngay c\u7843  tr\u7913 ng g\'e0 c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7853 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng \u273 i n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i trao \u273 \u7893 i nh\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c s\u7869  cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t kho\u7843 n h\u7885 c b\u7893 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 \'edt, h\u417 n n\u7919 a s\u7869  lo ph\'ed m\'e1y bay kh\u7913  h\u7891 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y m\u7895 i th\'e1ng s\u7869  ph\u7843 i t\u7889 n h\u417 n m\u7897 t ngh\'ecn \u273 \'f4 \'97\'97 ph\'ed \u259 n \u7903  m\u7897 t th\'e1ng c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n b\u7889 n n\u259 m trong n\u432 \u7899 c. H\u417 n n\u7919 a tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\'f2n c\'f3 nh\'e0 \u259 n gi\'e1 r\u7867 , m\u7895 i b\u7919 a kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m \u273 \u7891 ng \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u259 n r\u7845 t kh\'e1, d\'f9 c\'f3 ch\'e1n nh\'e0 \u259 n th\'ec c\'f2n c\'f3 \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n ngo\'e0i... L\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n t\'ednh \u432 u vi\u7879 t c\u7911 a \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c x\'e3 h\u7897 i ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a. B\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7853 u b\'e2y gi\u7901  v\u7851 n \u273 ang \u273 i h\u7885 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 thu nh\u7853 p, x\u7845 u h\u7893  ch\'eca tay xin cha m\u7865  qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u ti\u7873 n s\u7869  t\u7921  nhi\'ean h\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1ch t\'ednh to\'e1n chi li, h\u7885 c l\'e0m c\u417 m xem ra l\'e0 t\u7845 t y\u7871 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7875  thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n n\'ean l\'fac t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\u7853 u ch\u7881  mang theo qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7847 n m\u7863 c v\'e0 laptop, \u273 \u7891  d\'f9ng cho gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \u7891  l\'e0m b\u7871 p c\'f9ng v\u7899 i c\'e1c lo\u7841 i v\u7853 t d\u7909 ng h\'e0ng ng\'e0y to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7873 u c\u226 \u768 n mua m\u7899 i, c\'f2n ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m th\u7867  sinh vi\'ean, \u273 i ng\'e2n h\'e0ng m\u7903  t\'e0i kho\u7843 n, \u273 i l\'e0m sim v\'e0 v\'e9 xe bus... \u272 \u7911  lo\u7841 i vi\u7879 c kh\'e1c nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng may c\'f3 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, m\u7897 t bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u d\u7921 a theo th\u7913  t\u7921  c\u7847 n thi\u7871 t d\u7851 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i l\'e0m h\u7871 t, l\u7841 i d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i nh\u7853 n bi\u7871 t tr\u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7871 n khu trung t\'e2m mua s\u7855 m. \u272 \u7875  c\u7843 m \u417 n, sau khi mua \u273 \u7891  xong Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7901 i h\u7855 n \u259 n c\u417 m \u7903  nh\'e0 h\'e0ng Malaysia trong trung t\'e2m th\'e0nh ph\u7889 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7895  \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \u7873  c\u7917 , so ra m\'e0 n\'f3i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n kh\'e1 ngon v\'e0 r\u7867 , m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n c\u417 m ch\u7881  h\u417 n hai m\u432 \u417 i \u273 \'f4, nh\u432 ng rau th\u7883 t s\u7889  l\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7873 u t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7911 . Ph\u7847 n c\u417 m c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 c\'e0 ri g\'e0 v\'e0 c\'e0 ri t\'f4m, m\'f9i v\u7883  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , so v\u7899 i g\u7885 i \u273 \u7891  Trung th\'ec r\u7867  h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 May m\'e0 c\'f3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, m\u7897 t bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m xong c\u417  b\u7843 n nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c c\u7847 n l\'e0m, ch\u7881  c\'f2n th\u7867  ng\'e2n h\'e0ng ch\u432 a l\'e0m c\'f9ng v\u7899 i m\u7897 t \'edt \u273 \u7891  linh tinh ch\u432 a mua.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f9a khai gi\uc0\u7843 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\'e2n h\'e0ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i nhi\u7873 u, ph\u7843 i x\u7871 p h\'e0ng r\u7845 t l\'e2u, h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 i, thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t b\u7919 a tr\u432 a v\'e0 b\u7919 a t\u7889 i \u7903  subway trong tr\u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0 m\u7897 t ti\u7879 m g\'e0 chi\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i l\'fac v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac c\u7853 u g\u7863 p h\'e0ng x\'f3m \u7903  ph\'f2ng b\'ean tr\'e1i v\'e0 b\'ean ph\u7843 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u7903  ph\'f2ng 407, ph\'f2ng 406 b\'ean tr\'e1i l\'e0 m\u7897 t nam sinh t\'f3c \u273 en t\'ean Alex, th\'e2n cao tr\'ean m\u7897 t m\'e9t t\'e1m, da r\u7845 t tr\u7855 ng, c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7897  l\'ean c\u361 ng r\u7845 t r\u7921 c r\u7905 ; ph\'f2ng 408 b\'ean ph\u7843 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t n\u7919  sinh t\'ean Emily, m\'e1i t\'f3c v\'e0ng m\u7873 m m\u7841 i. T\u7915  ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh r\'f5 r\'e0ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u432 \u417 ng T\'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 n\uc0\u417 i n\'e0y ph\u7843 i xin x\'e9t v\'e0o, m\u7895 i n\u259 m h\u7885 c ho\u7863 c m\u7895 i h\u7885 c k\u7923  l\u7841 i ph\u7843 i xin m\u7899 i, c\u361 ng c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u sinh vi\'ean \u273 \'f4\u777 i k\'fd t\'fac ho\u7863 c l\'e0 chuy\u7875 n ra ngo\'e0i t\u7921  m\'ecnh thu\'ea nh\'e0 tr\u7885 . Emily c\u361 ng v\u7915 a chuy\u7875 n v\'e0o, n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7897 t l\'e1t li\u7873 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7891 , c\'f4 \u273 \'e3 h\u7865 n b\u7841 n c\'f9ng nhau \u259 n t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y l\'e0 c\u7853 u m\u7899 i \u273 \u7871 n h\'f4m qua \'e0?" Alex nh\'ecn c\u7853 u n\'f3i, "Sophus c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u n\u417 i hay ho, t\'f4i c\'f3 xe, c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i. C\u7853 u c\'f3 th\'edch t\u7909  h\u7885 p kh\'f4ng? B\u7885 n t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u bu\u7893 i ti\u7879 c th\'fa v\u7883  l\u7855 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t k\u7875  n\'f3i th\u7871  n\'e0o, s\u7921  th\u7853 t l\'e0 trong cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh vui t\u432 \u417 i s\u7869  d\u7877  chi\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7843 o c\u7843 m c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c h\u417 n, c\'f3 m\u7897 t h\'e0ng x\'f3m t\u7889 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n x\u7845 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i c\'e1m \u417 n v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, l\u7841 i t\'e1n g\u7851 u th\'eam hai c\'e2u m\u7899 i t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y th\uc0\u7913  ba l\u7841 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7847 y m\'e2y hi\u7871 m th\u7845 y, t\u7847 ng m\'e2y che khu\u7845 t \'e1nh m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i, s\u7855 c c\'e2y c\u361 ng hi\u7879 n v\u7867  t\u7889 i tr\u7847 m, c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng n\'e0y \u7903  th\'e1ng hai t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i \'edt th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean hai ng\'e0y tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c b\'f4n ba h\u417 i m\u7879 t, h\'f4m nay m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  s\'e1ng m\u7899 i r\u7901 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7855 t xe \u273 \u7871 n si\'eau th\u7883  g\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 c\u7849 n th\u7853 n ch\u7885 n l\u7921 a mua rau th\u7883 t nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  \u259 n, x\'e1ch v\u7873  mang v\'e0o b\u7871 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i th\uc0\u7853 t c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7869  l\'e0m m\'f3n g\'ec, b\'e8n mua m\u7897 t h\u7897 p tr\u7913 ng g\'e0, m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng th\u7883 t b\'f2 \u273 \'f3ng g\'f3i, n\u7917 a c\'e2y c\u7843 i tr\u7855 ng v\'e0 hai qu\u7843  c\'e0 chua, \'edt nh\u7845 t m\u7845 y th\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u th\u432 \u7901 ng g\u7863 p, kh\'f4ng kh\'f3 ch\u7871  bi\u7871 n l\u7855 m. \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng mu\u7889 i x\'ec d\u7847 u c\'e1c lo\u7841 i gia v\u7883  ng\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 d\u7851 n \u273 i si\'eau th\u7883  Trung Qu\u7889 c mua, tuy r\u7857 ng trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7889 ng b\u7897 t nh\'e3o, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 so v\u7899 i m\u7845 y ch\u7845 t h\'f3a h\u7885 c ph\u7843 i d\'f9ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, nh\u432 ng \'edt nh\u7845 t s\u7869  kh\'f4ng thi\u7871 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7895 i t\u7847 ng \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7889  tr\'ed hai ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p, trong b\u7871 p c\'f3 hai t\u7911  l\u7841 nh chung l\u7899 n v\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7911  \u273 \'e1, trong t\u7911  l\u7841 nh m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 v\u7883  tr\'ed thu\u7897 c v\u7873  m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f3a. V\u7883  tr\'ed t\u7911  l\u7841 nh c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  b\'ean tr\'e1i b\u7871 p, b\u7889 n ph\'eda b\u7871 p l\'e0 t\u7911  b\'e1t, b\u7891 n r\u7917 a, \u7903  gi\u7919 a l\'e0 hai h\'e0ng b\u7871 p g\u7891 m s\'e1u c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7845 y chi\u7871 c ch\u7843 o m\u7899 i mua ra \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean b\u7871 p, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n b\u7853 t gas. C\u7853 u quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u l\'e0m t\u7915  c\u417 m chi\'ean \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\'f9ng l\'f2 vi s\'f3ng h\u7845 p m\u7897 t ch\'e9n c\u417 m, th\'e1i s\u7907 i n\u7917 a c\'e2y c\u7843 i tr\u7855 ng, c\u7855 t c\'e0 chua h\u7841 t l\u7921 u, \u273 \u7853 p m\u7897 t qu\u7843  tr\u7913 ng g\'e0, r\u7845 t c\'f3 \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 em c\'e0 chua, n\u7917 a c\'e2y c\u7843 i tr\u7855 ng v\'e0 th\u7883 t b\'f2 c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o c\'f2n d\u432  l\u7841 i b\u7887  v\'e0o trong t\u7911  l\u7841 nh \'97\'97 c\u7853 u ngh\u297  ch\u7901  tr\'f9 ngh\u7879  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ti\u7871 n b\u7897 , n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m th\u7883 t b\'f2 h\u7847 m c\'e0 chua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'ean m\uc0\u7841 ng t\'ecm h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n l\'e0m c\u417 m chi\'ean, d\u7921 a theo c\'e1c b\u432 \u7899 c tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u273 \u7893  d\u7847 u v\'e0o \u273 \u7907 i cho s\'f4i, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7893  c\u417 m \u273 \'e3 h\u7845 p xong v\'e0o, ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i cho th\'eam c\u7843 i tr\u7855 ng, c\'e0 chua v\'e0 tr\u7913 ng g\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong h\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n n\'f3i l\'e0 cho th\'eam tr\u7913 ng v\'e0 h\'e0nh th\'e1i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c d\'f9 sao m\'ecnh c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i b\u7893  sung ch\'fat rau. C\u417 m m\u7899 i h\u7845 p xong h\'ecnh nh\u432  h\u417 i \u432 \u7899 t, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng m\u7845 y. Cho t\u7899 i gi\u7901  t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\u7847 n c\u7847 m mu\'f4i \u273 \u7843 o \u273 \u7843 o x\'e0o x\'e0o r\u7891 i th\'eam ch\'fat mu\u7889 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ph\'fat sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u7907 n m\u7855 t h\'e1 m\u7891 m nh\'ecn c\'e0 chua ra n\u432 \u7899 c, c\u7843 i tr\u7855 ng c\u361 ng ra n\u432 \u7899 c, trong n\u7891 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7889 ng h\u7891 ng \u273 \u7887  tr\u7855 ng ng\u7853 p n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t c\u7853 u gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t, l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i di \u273 \u7897 ng ra, r\u417 i v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\'f9ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7847 u vi\u7879 n Giang \u272 i\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  ch\u7889 c l\'e1t sau Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 t\u7915  l\u7847 u ba l\'ean, gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh nh\'ecn ch\u7843 o c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "... \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng may Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n bi\u7871 t tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean ph\u7843 i t\u7855 t l\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u417 m chi\'ean. B\u7887  th\'eam c\'e0 chua, c\u7843 i tr\u7855 ng, c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t qu\u7843  tr\u7913 ng g\'e0." C\u7853 u th\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng, m\u7897 t b\u7919 a c\u417 m ngay c\u7843  ch\'fat th\u7883 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'97\'97 b\u7903 i v\'ec kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean l\'e0m nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u417 m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u h\u7845 p h\u417 i qu\'e1 \u432 \u7899 t, h\u417 n n\u7919 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7843 i tr\u7855 ng r\u7845 t d\u7877  ra n\u432 \u7899 c, mu\u7889 n cho v\'e0o x\'e0o th\'ec \'edt nh\u7845 t tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 ph\u7843 i x\'e0o qua m\u7897 t l\u7847 n m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n nh\'ecn chi\u7871 c ch\u7843 o c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e0nh l\'f2ng: "Tr\'ec Di\'ean... C\'e1i n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\'f2n mu\u7889 n \u259 n kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7859 n l\'e0 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u259 n r\u7891 i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn ch\u7843 o, c\u7853 u h\u417 i ti\u7871 c qu\u7843  tr\u7913 ng kia, tr\u7913 ng g\'e0 c\u7853 u mua l\'e0 g\'e0 nu\'f4i th\u7843 , so v\u7899 i g\'e0 nu\'f4i nh\u7889 t \u273 \u7855 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng sao, \uc0\u273 \'fang d\u7883 p t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  n\u7871 m th\u7917  hamburger \u7903  nh\'e0 h\'e0ng c\u7853 u n\'f3i kia." C\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  n\'f3i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, l\u7841 i mi\'eau t\u7843  cho c\u7853 u v\u7883  tr\'ed ti\u7879 m hamburger kia m\u7897 t l\u7847 n: "T\'f4i \u259 n xong m\u7845 t r\u7891 i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng th\'ec c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7913 u t\u7871  c\u7853 u. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 th\u7871  n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao, m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 vi\u7879 c m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng gi\u7887 i, h\'e3y tin t\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n, v\u7907  t\u432 \u417 ng lai c\u7911 a c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  c\u7921 c k\'ec \u273 \u7843 m \u273 ang."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n gi\'fap c\u7853 u thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7889 ng l\u7897 n x\u7897 n trong b\u7871 p, sau \u273 \'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  l\u7847 u ba, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh l\u7845 y v\'ed \u273 i th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7879 m hamburger Giang \u272 i\u7873 n n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7879 m hamburger kia n\'f3i g\u7847 n c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 i h\u7871 t m\u7897 t con ph\u7889 , m\'e0 \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 ch\u7895  c\u7853 u th\u7871  m\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  b\'e1n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n n\'e0o kh\'e1c, c\u7853 u b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ho\'e0i ni\u7879 m \u272 \u7871  \u273 \'f4 n\u417 i n\u417 i c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng nh\'e0 h\'e0ng l\u7899 n l\u7899 n nh\u7887  nh\u7887 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i giao h\'e0ng m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  xanh v\'e0ng, so s\'e1nh ra n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y qu\u7843  th\u7921 c c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 n\'f4ng th\'f4n m\u7899 i c\u7911 a t\u432  b\u7843 n ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7841 i ho\'e1.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7879 m hamburger kia theo nh\u432  l\u7901 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n n\'f3i \u7849 n \u7903  m\u7863 t sau ph\u7889 , m\u7863 t ti\u7873 n r\u7845 t nh\u7887 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 ba b\u7889 n qu\u7847 y, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i cho kh\'e1ch, cho n\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  \u259 n ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  mang v\u7873 , nh\'ecn qua h\u417 i \u273 \u417 n s\u417 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong qu\uc0\u7847 y \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t \'edt th\u7913 c \u259 n chi\'ean, ph\'eda tr\'ean chi\u7871 u \u273 \'e8n s\'e1ng m\'e0u v\'e0ng \u7845 m; ph\'eda sau l\'e0 m\u7897 t ch\u7843 o d\u7847 u h\'ecnh vu\'f4ng v\u7851 n \u273 ang ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c, mang \u273 \u7871 n cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c d\u7847 u m\u7905  \u7845 m \'e1p d\u7877  ch\u7883 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u7903  m\u7863 t ti\u7873 n nh\u7887  h\u7865 p c\u7911 a c\u7917 a h\'e0ng c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\u7883  kh\'e1ch \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng trung ni\'ean t\'f3c x\'e1m, m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o s\u417 mi tr\u7855 ng, b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i l\'e0 qu\u7847 n t\'e2y \u273 en, thu h\'fat \'e1nh m\u259 \u769 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c ch\'ednh l\'e0 ngo\'e0i \'e1o s\u417 mi c\'f2n m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o gile k\u7867  \'f4 m\'e0u x\'e1m \'97\'97 m\'f9a n\'e0y \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y \u259 n m\u7863 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 h\u417 i k\u7923  qu\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n c\'f2n treo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891  qu\u7843  qu\'fdt \'e1nh kim, da m\u7863 t v\'e0 ph\u7847 n c\u7893  l\u7897  ra ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t tr\u7855 ng, kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng m\'e0u da c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i da tr\u7855 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch nh\u432  m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i b\u7879 nh tr\u7841 ng. Gi\'e0y c\u7911 a h\u7855 n r\u7845 t s\u7841 ch s\u7869 , th\u7871  \u273 \u7913 ng \u432 u nh\'e3, khi\u7871 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n th\'e2n s\u297  truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng trong phim \u7843 nh ph\u432 \u417 ng T\'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n v\'e0 ti\u7879 m hamburger n\'e0y kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u259 n kh\u7899 p nhau, l\'e0m Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i nh\'ecn nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n v\'e0i l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng c\u361 ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, quay \u273 \u7847 u g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u l\u7877  \u273 \u7897  c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, sau khi tr\u7843  ti\u7873 n xong li\u7873 n c\u7847 m \u273 \u7891  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 i ra. Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7883 ch sang tr\'e1i, nh\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u417 i g\'f3c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a b\'ean tr\'e1i nghe c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c xe h\u417 i m\'e0u \u273 en.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng c\u432 \u7899 c b\u7897  v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c xe, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean m\u7903  c\u7917 a xe gh\u7871  sau khom l\u432 ng \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7891  v\'e0o, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i quay l\u7841 i gh\u7871  \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7903  c\u7917 a ng\u7891 i v\'e0o. \u272 \u7897 ng t\'e1c khom l\u432 ng kia khi\u7871 n h\u7855 n c\'f3 v\u7867  khi\'eam t\u7889 n m\'e0 cung k\'ednh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat t\'f2 m\'f2, v\'ec v\uc0\u7853 y kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7851 n ng\'f3 ch\u7915 ng nh\'ecn, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'e0nh vi c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7845 t l\u7877  hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  m\u7903  c\u7917 a \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7891  v\'e0o kia, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y h\'ecnh d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i \u7903  gh\u7871  sau. \u272 \'f3 h\u7859 n l\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t nam nh\'e2n, b\u7903 i v\'ec tuy r\u7857 ng ch\u7881  trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t, c\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\'ecn th\u7845 y t\u7915  trong v\u432 \u417 n ra m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay tr\u7855 ng x\'e1m m\'e0 thon d\'e0i\'97\'97 thon d\'e0i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i to r\u7897 ng h\u7919 u l\u7921 c, kh\u7899 p x\u432 \u417 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c tr\'e0n \u273 \u7847 y s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\uc0\u7843  n\u259 ng l\'e0 tay ph\u7909  n\u7919  cho l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'f3n tay h\uc0\u7855 n h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 eo v\u7853 t g\'ec \u273 \'f3, tho\'e1ng c\'e1i l\'e0m ch\'f3i m\u7855 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m t\u7883 t m\u7855 t, l\'fac m\u7903  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn l\u7841 i th\'ec chi\u7871 c xe h\u417 i m\'e0u \u273 en kia \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t n\u417 i g\'f3c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
