\cb3 Emily th\'ec th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\'f9ng c\'e1c b\u7841 n n\u7919  n\u432 \u7899 ng b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t ho\u7863 c b\'e1nh quy. H\'f4m nay c\'f4 l\'e0m m\'ec \'dd, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n cho c\'f4 m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n c\'e1nh g\'e0 c\u7853 u ta l\'e0m, \u273 \u7875  coi nh\u432  c\'f3 qua c\'f3 l\u7841 i, c\'f4 c\u361 ng l\u7845 y hai ph\u7847 n nh\u7887  \u273 \u7891  m\'ecnh l\'e0m chia cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n. Trong si\'eau th\u7883  th\u432 \u7901 ng b\'e1n c\'e1c lo\u7841 i m\'ec \u7889 ng \u273 \'f3ng g\'f3i, sau khi mua v\u7873  n\u7845 u th\'eam ch\'fat gia v\u7883  l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n sinh vi\'ean \u7903  \u273 \'e2y th\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7897 t s\u7889  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 n\'f3i, kh\u7843  n\u259 ng n\u7845 u \u259 n l\u7853 t ch\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 o mu\'f4i c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n th\u7847 n k\u7923  t\u7921 a nh\u432  \u7843 o thu\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\'f4m nay \uc0\u259 n th\u7883 t chu\u7897 t t\'fai." Emily ch\u7881  m\u7897 t kh\u7889 i m\'ec \'dd d\'ednh s\u7879 t gi\u7843 i th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u259 n th\u7883 t chu\u7897 t t\'fai, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd l\'e0 trong si\'eau th\u7883  c\'f3 b\'e1n. Nh\u432 ng th\u7847 y gi\'e1o d\u7841 y l\u7883 ch s\u7917  th\u7901 i T\u7847 n H\'e1n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i, th\u7853 t ra th\u7901 i k\u7923  T\u7847 n H\'e1n, ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'e2n g\u7863 p lo\'e0i g\'ec th\'ec \u259 n lo\'e0i \u273 \'f3, bay tr\'ean tr\u7901 i ch\u7841 y d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t b\u417 i trong n\u432 \u7899 c c\'e1c lo\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng g\'ec ki\'eang k\u7925 . Nh\u432 ng v\u7873  sau tr\u7843 i qua h\u417 n ng\'e0n n\u259 m ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n, m\'f4i tr\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'ed h\u7853 u tr\'ean \u273 \u7845 t li\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 thay \u273 \u7893 i r\u7845 t l\u7899 n, th\'f3i quen \u7849 m th\u7921 c theo \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng bi\u7871 n h\'f3a r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, th\u7901 i gian d\u7847 n tr\'f4i, nh\u7919 ng nguy\'ean li\u7879 u n\u7845 u \u259 n nh\u432  chim s\'e2u r\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i b\'e0n \u259 n, ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c n\u7845 u n\u432 \u7899 ng c\u361 ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 i\u7873 u ch\u7881 nh v\'e0 c\u7843 i bi\u7871 n. Nh\u432 ng khu v\u7921 c ph\'eda nam sau c\'f9ng, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  Qua\u777 ng \u272 \'f4ng, h\u417 n ngh\'ecn n\u259 m qua kh\'ed h\u7853 u m\'f4i tr\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fat thay \u273 \u7893 i, v\'ec v\u7853 y r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u7849 m th\u7921 c truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ecn gi\u7919  l\u432 u l\u7841 i, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  \u259 n c\'e1, r\u7855 n, *\u273 \u7889 t t\u7883 ch c\'e1c lo\u7841 i, c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i *L\u297 nh Nam Vi\u7879 t th\u7853 t ra ch\'ednh l\'e0 ho\'e1 th\u7841 ch s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a \u7849 m th\u7921 c Trung Hoa truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng.\cb1 \

