\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng nh\u7887 , r\'e1ch \'edt da th\u7883 t b\'ean ngo\'e0i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'e1n b\u259 ng c\'e1 nh\'e2n xong l\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ki\'ean c\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7903  l\u7841 i b\u7871 p b\'e0o khoai t\'e2y s\u7907 i, nh\u432 ng c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ch\u7881  trong th\u7901 i gian ng\u7855 n nh\u432  th\u7871 , Alex v\u7899 i b\'f2 b\'edt t\u7871 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
