\cb3 Ngo\'e0i c\uc0\u7917 a truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7885 ng Alex: "Jerry, Jerry, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ng\u7911  ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
