\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y tr\'ean m\u7841 ng nh\u7919 ng b\'e0i b\'e1o v\u7873  ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0 \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 c\'e1c lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t hoang d\'e3 nh\u432  s\'f3i, g\u7845 u chung s\u7889 ng h\'e0i h\'f2a \u7903  nh\u7919 ng th\'e0nh th\u7883  c\'f3 sinh th\'e1i t\u7889 t, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u quanh khu m\'ecnh s\u7889 ng c\'f3 th\'fa d\u7919  t\u7845 n c\'f4ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec v\u7851 n h\u417 i khi\u7871 n l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u417 i ho\u7843 ng.\cb1 \
