\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng c\'e1c th\'e0nh vi\'ean trong nh\'f3m th\uc0\u7843 o lu\u7853 n \u273 \u7871 n n\u259 m gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u. C\u7853 u ngh\u297  h\'f4m nay l\'e0 th\u7913  b\u7843 y, l\u7841 i v\u7915 a khai gi\u7843 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e2u, c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m, nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i trong k\'fd t\'fac kia nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  m\u7903  party \u7903  l\u7847 u n\u259 m, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh l\u7841 i s\u7869  b\u7883  l\'e0m cho c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7853 u b\'e8n d\u7913 t kho\'e1t \u7903  l\u7841 i th\u432  vi\u7879 n, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n ch\'edn gi\u7901  m\u7899 i thu d\u7885 n c\u7863 p s\'e1ch tr\u7903  v\u7873 .\cb1 \
