\cb3 "Jerry, Jerry!"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe th\uc0\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng g\u7885 i \u7847 m \u297  v\'e0 ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n, m\u7897 t l\'e1t m\u7899 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng ra l\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 ang g\u7885 i m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, v\u7915 a v\u7863 n tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y Alex \u273 ang \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
