\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7915 a \u273 i v\u7873  k\'ed t\'fac x\'e1, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i t\u7889 i nh\u432  m\u7921 c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng t\u7887 a ra \'e1nh s\'e1ng m\'e0u cam l\u417 \u768  m\u417 \u768 , khi\u7871 n b\'f3ng b\u7909 i c\u7887  b\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng k\'e9o d\'e0i th\u7853 t d\'e0i. B\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i t\u7855 t qua m\u7897 t con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 ang \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a hai t\'f2a nh\'e0, con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 ng\u7855 n, l\u7841 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7921 a v\'e0o \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u7903  hai b\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n h\u7855 t v\'e0o chi\u7871 u s\'e1ng, cho n\'ean c\'e0ng c\'f3 v\u7867  t\u7889 i t\u259 m.\cb1 \
