\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n \u273 ang \u273 i \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean t\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7853 u ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Alex c\'e0ng \u273 i c\'e0ng c\'e1ch m\'ecnh g\u7847 n. L\'fac n\'e0y b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 o\u7841 n gi\u7919 a con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, Alex l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean d\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c, quay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
