\cb3 Alex trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t h\'ecnh nh\u432  h\u417 i s\u7919 ng l\u7841 i, m\u7897 t gi\'e2y sau l\u7841 i c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c \u273 \u7913 ng th\u7859 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean. Gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  s\u432  t\u7917  \u273 ang chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u259 n th\u7883 t con m\u7891 i l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\'f3 k\u7867  kh\'e1c \u273 ang ng\u7845 p ngh\'e9.\cb1 \
