\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Tom h\u7891 i \'e2m r\u7845 t nhanh: "Th\u7853 t l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e1i t\'ean \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i g\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7913 ng l\u7841 i, c\u7853 u c\'f3 n\'ean khen \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\u7845 t l\u7883 ch s\u7921  kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e2y?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, g\'f5: "T\'ean ti\u7871 ng Anh c\u7911 a anh r\u7845 t \'eam tai."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7889  \'fd t\'e1n d\u432 \u417 ng, m\'e0 l\'e0 th\u7853 t l\'f2ng cho r\u7857 ng nh\u432  th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi... L\u7863 p \u273 i l\u7863 p l\u7841 i c\'e1i t\'ean n\'e0y, li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7873 m l\'f2ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng. Th\u7853 t s\u7921 , c\u7921 c k\'ec \'eam tai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i li\'ean t\u7909 c tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n, b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c \u273 \'e3 h\u417 n hai ti\u7871 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\'ean l\u7847 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng, party \u273 \'e3 k\u7871 t th\'fac.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t r\u432 \u7905 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n cho c\u7853 u n\'f3i "Mu\u7897 n r\u7891 i, c\u7853 u \u273 i ng\u7911  \u273 i. Ng\u7911  ngon.", Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7901 i gian th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7899 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh c\uc0\u361 ng v\u7853 y, ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i s\u7899 m ch\'fat. Ng\u7911  ngon." C\u7853 u m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i \u7845 n "G\u7917 i \u273 i", kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra t\'e2m t\'ecnh m\u7897 t ng\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh b\u7903 i v\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n m\u7899 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n th\u7853 m ch\'ed ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p m\u7863 t n\'e0y m\'e0 tr\u7903  n\'ean d\u7877  ch\u7883 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  \u273 \'f3 v\u7873  sau hai ng\u432 \u7901 i duy tr\'ec li\'ean l\u7841 c nh\u7855 n tin m\u7895 i ng\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng h\u7887 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'ecnh ph\u7843 i l\'e0m g\'ec \u273 \u7875  gi\'fap h\u7855 n h\u7885 c ti\u7871 ng Trung, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tho\u7843 i m\'e1i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "T\'f4i cho r\u7857 ng h\u7885 c ngo\u7841 i ng\u7919  quan tr\u7885 ng nh\u7845 t l\'e0 ph\u7843 i th\u7921 c h\'e0nh, v\u7853 y n\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7847 n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i t\'f4i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i ~ hy v\u7885 ng c\u7853 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\'ea t\'f4i phi\u7873 n [ngh\u7883 ch ng\u7907 m]."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c sau nh\u432  m\u7897 t th\'eam v\'e0o cu\u7889 i c\'e2u m\u7897 t icon \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau cho m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\u7875  cho c\u7853 u n\u417 i \u7903  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u7903  ch\'e2u \'c2u, h\u7855 n n\'f3i \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t trang vi\'ean r\u7845 t l\u7899 n, b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u7903  trong m\u7897 t l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i c\u7893  c\'f3 l\u7883 ch s\u7917  h\u417 n m\u7897 t ngh\'ecn n\u259 m, hoa vi\'ean trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i c\'f3 \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i hoa h\u7891 ng \u273 \u7887  tr\u7855 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kho\'e1c l\'e1c h\uc0\u7843 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong b\u7909 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  tin t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, theo s\'e1ch gi\'e1o khoa l\u7883 ch s\u7917 , gi\u7899 i qu\'fd t\u7897 c truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng ch\'e2u \'c2u \u273 \'e3 suy vong t\u7915  l\u7847 n c\'e1ch m\u7841 ng c\'f4ng nghi\u7879 p \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean, hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7841 i n\u7855 m gi\u7919  ti\u7873 n t\'e0i quy\u7873 n th\u7871  \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883  to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 t\u432  b\u7843 n. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\'e1i tu\u7893 i n\'e0y thanh ni\'ean t\'ednh t\'ecnh n\'f3ng n\u7843 y b\u7897 p ch\u7897 p th\'edch khoe khoang c\'f3 v\u7867  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\u7853 t x\u7845 u qu\'e1 l\u7899 n, quanh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u th\'edch kho\'e1c l\'e1c, khuy\u7871 t \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f4ng che l\u7845 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u432 u \u273 i\u7875 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  ph\u7909  h\u7885 a n\'f3i: "V\u7853 y th\u7853 t l\'e0 t\u7889 t, c\'f3 c\u417  h\u7897 i em c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n \u273 i xem th\u7917 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u th\'edch kh\'f4ng?" \u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\'e0o h\u7913 ng b\u7915 ng b\u7915 ng truy v\u7845 n, m\u7897 t l\'e1t sau l\u7841 i g\u7917 i hai t\u7845 m h\'ecnh qua, "C\u7853 u xem, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 n\u417 i t\'f4i hay \u7903  nh\u7845 t, may m\'e0 qu\u7843 n gia t\u7889 t c\'f2n gi\u7919  \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p \u7903  \u273 \'f3, t\'f4i v\u7915 a b\u7843 o \'f4ng \u7845 y g\u7917 i cho t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7842 nh ch\u7909 p ban ng\'e0y, m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i s\'e1ng r\u7921 c r\u7905 , tr\u7901 i xanh kh\'f4ng m\'e2y. Qu\u7843  nhi\'ean gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mi\'eau t\u7843 , m\u7897 t t\'f2a l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en nguy nga t\u7885 a l\u7841 c ph\'eda sau t\u7847 ng t\u7847 ng hoa h\u7891 ng tr\u7855 ng lay \u273 \u7897 ng, trang tr\u7885 ng m\'e0 nghi\'eam t\'fac, hoa m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng l\u7841 i v\'ec v\u7853 y m\'e0 t\u259 ng th\'eam v\'e0i ph\u7847 n m\u7873 m m\u7841 i xinh \u273 \u7865 p. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng h\u7885 c ki\u7871 n tr\'fac, kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ra n\'f3 thu\u7897 c v\u7873  th\u7901 i k\u7923  n\'e0o phong c\'e1ch g\'ec, ch\u7881  tr\u7921 c quan c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\'f3 \u273 \u7891  s\u7897  l\u7841 i th\u7847 n b\'ed.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 ch\u7895  \u7903  hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a t\'f4i, c\u361 ng l\'e0 n\u417 i t\'f4i \u7903  l\'e2u nh\u7845 t, t\'f4i c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7845 y ch\u7895  \u7903  kh\'e1c, \u273 \'e1ng ti\u7871 c hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p, mu\u7889 n th\'ec ph\u7843 i \u273 i t\'ecm qu\u7843 n gia h\u7887 i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7875  cho c\u7853 u xem c\u7853 u th\'edch n\u417 i n\'e0o nh\u7845 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7895  n\'e0y em c\u361 ng r\u7845 t th\'edch, hoa r\u7845 t \u273 \u7865 p." Nh\'ecn ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7911  nh\'e2n hao t\'e2m t\u7893 n tr\'ed m\'e0 qu\u7843 n l\'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ho\'e0n to\'e0n tin l\u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, b\u7841 n c\'f9ng ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 ang h\u7885 c trao \u273 \u7893 i \u7903  ch\'e2u \'c2u, trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u361 ng l\u432 u m\u7897 t \u273 \u7889 ng \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i Neuschwanstein. B\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng t\u7899 i ch\'e2u \'c2u, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nghi\'ean c\u7913 u ki\u7871 n tr\'fac ch\'e2u \'c2u, cho d\'f9 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7921 c s\u7921  l\u7845 y \u7843 nh l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i Neuschwanstein cho m\'ecnh xem r\u7891 i c\u7913  th\u7871  n\'f3i l\'e0 nh\'e0 h\u7855 n, m\'ecnh c\u361 ng ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e3 ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i quen th\'e2n mu\u7889 n xem nh\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 m\u7845 y ph\'f2ng, m\u7895 i ph\'f2ng \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n th\u7871  n\'e0o, \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3i l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta l\'e0m kh\'e1ch, m\'ecnh v\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f2n ch\u432 a h\u7859 n s\u7869  th\u7853 t s\u7921  g\u7863 p m\u7863 t, nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n qu\'e1 t\'edch c\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y hai tu\u7847 n sau khi c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7855 n tin tr\'ean m\u7841 ng, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\'edch n\'f3i m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n "Kho\'e1c l\'e1c" kh\'f4ng h\u7907 p v\u7899 i th\u7921 c t\u7871  cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng ra, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng th\'edch ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n ch\u7881  g\u7863 p tr\'ean m\u7841 ng n\'e0y, n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7845 t h\u7907 p \'fd, c\u361 ng r\u7845 t tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, h\u7855 n lu\'f4n c\'f3 c\'e1ch l\'e0m m\'ecnh tr\u7903  n\'ean vui v\u7867 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean khi \uc0\u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u7887 i c\u7853 u s\u7889  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921  \u273 \u432 a cho h\u7855 n \'97\'97 vi\u7879 c n\'e0y v\'e0 vi\u7879 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  ti\u7875 u h\u7885 c c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u7841 y "Kh\'f4ng n\'ean d\u7877  d\'e0ng tin ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841  tr\'ean m\u7841 ng", "Kh\'f4ng n\'ean t\'f9y ti\u7879 n \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  th\'f4ng tin c\'e1 nh\'e2n" qu\u7843  th\u7921 c l\'e0 \u273 i ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 c k\u7879  \u273 i, d\'f9 sao \u273 \'e2y ch\u7881  l\'e0 s\u7889  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u7903  \'dac c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, ch\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n khi v\u7873  n\u432 \u7899 c kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  b\u7883  c\u7855 t kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai m\uc0\u432 \u417 i gi\'e2y sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7917 i s\u7889  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u273 i, di \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u vang l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 m\uc0\u7897 t d\'e3y s\u7889  l\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u7903  ch\'e2u \'dac quen bi\u7871 t c\'f3 h\u7841 n, li\'ean h\u7879  v\u7899 i gi\'e1o vi\'ean v\'e0 c\'e1c b\u7841 n h\u7885 c th\'ec th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'f4ng qua email ho\u7863 c tin nh\u7855 n, c\u417  b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho c\u7853 u. L\'fac \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i vang l\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 tho\'e1ng \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7889  n\'e0y thu\u7897 c v\u7873  ai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'f3n tay c\uc0\u7853 u h\u417 i ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, nh\u7845 n nghe tr\'ean m\'e0n h\'ecnh, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u432 a \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i l\'ean tai.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ean kia truy\uc0\u7873 n t\u7899 i m\u7897 t gi\u7885 ng nam tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p m\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 m \u273 \u7841 m, so v\u7899 i t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\'f2n d\u7877  nghe h\u417 n. \'c2m s\u7855 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'e3nh t\u297 nh m\'e0 th\'e0nh th\u7909 c, nghe v\'e0o tai ho\'e0n to\'e0n b\u7845 t \u273 \u7891 ng v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Tom th\'edch g\u7917 i c\'e1c lo\u7841 i icon b\'e1n manh ngh\u7883 ch ng\u7907 m cho m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i ngh\uc0\u297  l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac n\'ean nh\u7901  c\u7853 u gi\'fap t\'f4i s\u7917 a ph\'e1t \'e2m r\u7891 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng n\'f3i, trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i tho\'e1ng ch\u7913 a \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe thanh \'e2m n\'e0y, m\'e1 tr\'e1i g\uc0\u7847 n s\'e1t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\'f4 h\'ecnh n\'f3ng l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean \u273 \'f4\u777 i di \u273 \u7897 ng sang tay ph\u7843 i \'97\'97 hai b\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 i x\u7917  nh\u432  nhau ha.\cb1 \
