\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi hay g\u7885 i t\u7899 i l\'fac m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  t\u7889 i, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng l\'fac \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a t\u7855 m xong, c\u7853 u s\u7869  m\u7903  c\u7917 a s\u7893 , v\u7915 a n\'f3i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\u7915 a h\'f3ng gi\'f3 \u273 \u7875  t\'f3c kh\'f4. Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n t\u7915  n\u7917 a gi\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t gi\u7901 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  n\'f3i ti\u7871 ng Anh v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, c\u361 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  gi\'fap c\u7853 u s\u7917 a l\u7841 i m\u7897 t \'edt v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  ph\'e1t \'e2m v\'e0 kh\u7849 u \'e2m. N\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t th\'fa v\u7883  l\u7841 i c\'f2n th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 l\u7907 i v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean r\u7845 t th\'edch n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\uc0\u7849 u \'e2m c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi Anh t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i ch\'ednh c\u7889 ng, l\'fac n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n lu\'f4n c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\u7845 t sang, lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y khi n\'f3i ra mi\u7879 ng l\u7841 i c\'e0ng l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. L\'fac nghe h\u7855 n n\'f3i ti\u7871 ng Trung kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y sao, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac nghe \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i ti\u7871 ng Anh Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\u7843 i t\'e2\u803 p trung g\u7845 p b\u7897 i \u273 \u7875  nghe xem \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i \u273 ang n\'f3i g\'ec, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7873 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y v\'e0nh tai n\'f3ng l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7853 u hi\u7875 u v\'ec sao c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i so s\'e1nh ti\u7871 ng Anh nh\u432  \'e2m thanh quy\u7871 n r\u361  ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 i h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 t\u7847 m tr\u432 \u7899 c sau m\u432 \u7901 i r\u432 \u7905 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nghe th\u7845 y b\'ean ngo\'e0i vang l\'ean ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a v\'e0 ti\u7871 ng g\u7885 i t\'ean c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe gi\uc0\u7885 ng l\'e0 Alex.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i v\'e0o \uc0\u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i: "Ch\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'ecm em."\cb1 \
