\cb3 Tr\'ean tay Alex c\uc0\u7847 m hai t\u7845 m thi\u7879 p m\'e0u \u273 en m\u7841  v\'e0ng "N\'e0y, Jerry, cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n n\'e0y c\'f3 m\u7897 t ti\u7879 c r\u432 \u7907 u do c\'f4ng ty Prius t\u7893  ch\u7913 c. B\'e2y gi\u7901  t\'f4i \u273 ang th\u7921 c t\u7853 p \u7903  \u273 \'f3 n\'ean l\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng \'edt thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i, b\u7885 n h\u7885  r\u7845 t hoan ngh\'eanh sinh vi\'ean AHU c\'f3 m\u7863 t, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\u417  h\u7897 i t\u7889 t \u273 \u7875  qu\u7843 ng b\'e1 c\'f4ng ty. C\u7853 u mu\u7889 n th\u7875  nghi\u7879 m m\u7897 t Sophus kh\'e1c v\u7899 i nhi\u7873 u ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 a d\u7841 ng \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? \u272 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\u417  h\u7897 i t\u7889 t, ch\u7895  t\'f4i c\'f3 hai t\u7845 m thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  mang ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n kia c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 i c\'f9ng. C\u7853 u ta t\'ean g\'ec nh\u7881 ? Kevin h\u7843 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Kevin l\'e0 t\'ean ti\uc0\u7871 ng Anh c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915  khi t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y v\u7851 n ch\u432 a tham gia bu\u7893 i ti\u7879 c ch\'ednh th\u7913 c n\'e0o, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 ch\'fat h\u7913 ng th\'fa \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ti\u7879 c r\u432 \u7907 u n\'e0y, v\'ec v\u7853 y s\u7843 ng kho\'e1i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\u7843 m \u417 n \'fd t\u7889 t c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. C\u7853 u nh\u7853 n thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i, n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, c\'e1m \u417 n c\u7853 u, t\'f4i s\u7869  h\u7887 i Kevin xem sao."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'e1c c\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7899 i v\u7853 y th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\u7889 t qu\'e1 r\u7891 i, " Alex h\'e0o s\u7843 ng c\u432 \u7901 i, "\u272 \u7883 a \u273 i\u7875 m bu\u7893 i ti\u7879 c c\'e1ch k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 h\u417 i xa, t\'f4i v\'e0 \u273 \'e1m Simon s\u7869  l\'e1i xe \u273 i. C\u7853 u v\u7899 i Kevin c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7891 i xe c\u7911 a t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i c\u7843 m \u417 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\u7847 n n\u7919 a r\u7891 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fac ng\u7911  ngon, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a tr\u7903  l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean b\'e0n, m\'e0n h\'ecnh s\'e1ng, cu\u7897 c tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n v\u7851 n \u273 ang k\u7871 t n\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh \uc0\u273 \'e3 nghe th\u7845 y ch\u432 a? B\u7841 n h\u7885 c ph\'f2ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\u7901 i em cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n n\'e0y tham gia m\u7897 t bu\u7893 i ti\u7879 c. Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t r\u432 \u7907 u \u7903  \u273 \'f3 s\u7869  l\'e0 lo\u7841 i g\'ec \u273 \'e2y, anh \u273 \'e3 \u273 i bao gi\u7901  ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7907 c: " B\u7841 n h\u7885 c ph\'f2ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh? L\'e0 nam sinh m\u7855 t xanh t\'f3c \u273 en th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean l\'eau l\u7893 ng v\u7899 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m b\u7841 n c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i t\'f4i sao? T\'f4i khuy\'ean c\u7853 u n\'ean h\u7841 n ch\u7871  ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 , nghe v\'e0o tai t\'f4i th\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ho\'e0ng g\'ec c\u7843 ." Trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\u7897  ra ch\'fat kh\'f4ng h\'e0i l\'f2ng hi\u7871 m th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, em bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i b\u7843 o th\u7911  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7853 u c\'f2n t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng thanh ni\'ean n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7873 u t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i c\u7903 i m\u7903 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y gi\u7889 ng h\u7879 t nh\u432  th\u7847 y ch\u7911  nhi\u7879 m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  vui ch\u417 i th\'f4i m\'e0, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t t\u7889 t. \u7902  n\u432 \u7899 c em c\u361 ng c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u b\u7841 n h\u7885 c l\'fac b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng thong th\u7843  nh\'e0n r\u7895 i, \u273 \u7871 n khi n\u432 \u7899 c t\u7899 i ch\'e2n m\u7899 i nh\u7843 y nh\u432 ng th\'e0nh t\'edch v\u7851 n r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7895  l\u7921 c b\u7857 ng c\'e1ch kh\'e1c nhau m\'e0. H\u417 n n\u7919 a l\u7847 n n\'e0y em c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng c\u7853 u ta r\u7891 i, ch\u7881  \u273 i xem th\u7917 , kh\'f4ng u\u7889 ng qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u r\u432 \u7907 u n\'ean h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng sao \u273 \'e2u. Prius c\u361 ng l\'e0 c\'f4ng ty r\u7845 t n\u7893 i danh m\'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Prius l\'e0 m\uc0\u7897 t c\'f4ng ty c\'f4ng ngh\u7879  sinh h\u7885 c, r\u7845 t n\u7893 i ti\u7871 ng \u7903  \'dac. L\'e3nh th\u7893  \'dac b\u7903 i v\'ec m\'f4i tr\u432 \u7901 ng ,v\u7883  tr\'ed \u273 \u7883 a l\'fd c\'f9ng qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh thay \u273 \u7893 i t\u7921  nhi\'ean \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t m\'e0 c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 \'f4\u803 ng th\u7921 c v\u7853 t k\u7923  di\u7879 u n\u417 i B\u7855 c b\'e1n c\u7847 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3, trong ng\'e0nh c\'f4ng ngh\u7879  sinh h\u7885 c, v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  \u273 i\u7873 u ch\u7871  thu\u7889 c b\u7843 o v\u7879  s\u7913 c kho\u7867  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\'f3 \u432 u th\u7871  d\u7851 n \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i v\u7915 a l\u7853 t xem thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i Alex \u273 \u432 a. Thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i thi\u7871 t k\u7871  c\u7921 c k\u7923  tinh x\u7843 o, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n mang theo h\u432 \u417 ng th\u417 m thoang tho\u7843 ng \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t. M\u7863 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0u \u273 en, ph\'eda tr\'ean in hoa v\u259 n m\'e0u v\'e0ng, l\u7853 t ra sau l\'e0 ch\u7919  m\u7841  v\'e0ng bay b\u432 \u7899 m\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7901 i b\u7841 n tham gia th\u7883 nh y\u7871 n tu\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u7911 a ch\'fang t\'f4i, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh b\u7841 n s\u7869  c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam kh\'f3 qu\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i ghi ch\'fa r\'f5 th\u7901 i gian \u273 \u7883 a \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7911 a bu\u7893 i ti\u7879 c. Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7919  k\'ed r\'f5 r\'e0ng, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7885 c c\'e0ng mu\u7889 n tham gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi sau khi nghe c\u7853 u n\'f3i xong ch\u7881  kh\u7869  "\u7914 m" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ng\u259 n c\u7843 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
