\cb3 "B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 ch\'fang ta v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i ch\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, v\u7851 n c\'f2n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i." Alex m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i, nh\'ecn t\'e2m t\'ecnh c\'f3 v\u7867  r\u7845 t t\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e1t sau Emily m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c v\'e1y tr\u7855 ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t ba ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\u7897 t \u273 \u7847 u t\'f3c v\'e0ng xinh \u273 \u7865 p c\u7911 a c\'f4 bu\u7897 c cao l\'ean, tr\'ean tay mang theo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c t\'fai x\'e1ch nh\u7887  m\'e0u tr\'e2n ch\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'ec ra ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i Alex mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7907 i l\'e0 Emily, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 vi\u7879 c n\'e0y c\u361 ng d\u7877  gi\u7843 i th\'edch, d\'f9 sao b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7889 ng r\u7845 t g\u7847 n nhau, nh\'ecn qua quan h\u7879  gi\u7919 a Alex v\'e0 Emily c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 . N\u7871 u \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 m\u7901 i m\'ecnh th\'ec \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng s\u7869  m\u7901 i Emily.\cb1 \
\cb3 "M\'e0u tr\uc0\u7855 ng, r\u7845 t \u273 \u7865 p. B\u7885 n h\u7885  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  th\'edch." Alex nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng ca ng\u7907 i, mang theo ba ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean xe. Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n ng\u7891 i \u7903  gh\u7871  sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sophus ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\'f3 \uc0\u273 i\u7875 m t\u7889 t n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'e3 l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng b\u7883  k\u7865 t xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex l\'e1i xe m\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7841 y ra ngo\u7841 i \'f4\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'ean ti\u7871 ng h\u7887 i: "Tr\'ean thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i vi\u7871 t bu\u7893 i ti\u7879 c t\u7893  ch\u7913 c \u7903  ph\'eda t\'e2y th\'e0nh ph\u7889  sao? Sao l\u7841 i ch\u7841 y ra ph\'eda \u273 \'f4ng?" L\'fac c\'f2n \u273 i h\u7885 c h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng tham gia m\u7897 t h\u7897 i ngh\u7883  h\u7885 c thu\u7853 t do tr\u432 \u7901 ng t\u7893  ch\u7913 c, v\'ec v\u7853 y c\'f2n nh\u7899  r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7871 n h\'f4m qua th\'ec \u273 \u7893 i l\u7841 i \u273 \u7883 a \u273 i\u7875 m, " Alex \u273 \'e1p, "N\'f3i th\u7853 t, t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7841 i sao b\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7893 i \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7881 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7879 c r\u432 \u7907 u t\u7893  ch\u7913 c \u7903  m\u7897 t trang vi\'ean v\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i th\'e0nh, c\'e1ch n\u417 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 xa, \'f4 t\'f4 ch\u7841 y m\u7897 t gi\u7901  l\'e0 t\u7899 i n\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex d\uc0\u7855 t tay Emily \u273 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng l\u7849 m b\u7849 m v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "C\u7853 u \u273 \'fang l\'e0 qu\'e1 k\'e9m, c\u7853 u nh\'ecn Alex xem c\u7853 u ta kh\'f4n ngoan bao nhi\'eau, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7851 n b\u7841 n g\'e1i \u273 \u7871 n m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i mang t\'f4i \u273 i c\'f9ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\uc0\u7843 i m\'e1i v\u7895  v\u7895  vai h\u7855 n: "Kh\'f4ng n\'ean t\u7921  coi nh\u7865  m\'ecnh."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Alex v\uc0\u7915 a \u273 i v\'e0o h\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng kh\'ed kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\'edu nh\'edu m\'e0y, t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Simon \u273 ang \'f4m m\u7897 t thi\u7871 u ni\'ean nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i t\'e1n t\u7881 nh, c\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7841 nh t\'fam Simon qua m\u7897 t b\'ean, h\u7841  gi\u7885 ng nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i: "X\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec th\u7871 ? Sao l\u7841 i c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u l\'e3o gia h\u7887 a t\u7899 i th\u7871  n\'e0y? Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\'e2u kh\'f4ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t y\u7871 n h\u7897 i m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i tr\u259 ng tr\'f2n c\u7911 a m\u7897 t c\'e1 nh\'e2n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, sao l\u7841 i h\u7845 p d\u7851 n nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7897 c l\u7899 n tu\u7893 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y? H\u7855 n nh\'ecn s\u417  qua m\u7897 t v\'f2ng, c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7845 y g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng thu\u7897 c v\u7873  Sophus. N\u7871 u h\u7855 n nh\u7899  kh\'f4ng l\u7847 m th\'ec nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia h\u7859 n l\'e0 c\u7889  \'fd t\u7915  Sydney ho\u7863 c Melbourne t\u7899 i, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'f2n \u273 \u7871 n t\u7915  Adelaide v\'e0 nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng l\'e3o gia h\u7887 a kia c\u7909 ng r\u432 \u7907 u, th\'ec th\u7847 m v\u7899 i nhau, th\u7847 n t\'ecnh c\u7917  ch\u7881  \u273 \u7873 u mang theo v\'e0i ph\u7847 n t\u7853 n l\u7921 c trang tr\u7885 ng nghi\'eam t\'fac.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0, th\u7901 i Trung C\u7893  \u273 \'e3 qua bao l\'e2u r\u7891 i ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex s\uc0\u7889 t ru\u7897 t k\'e9o c\u7893  \'e1o s\u417  mi, hy v\u7885 ng h\u7843 o h\u7919 u c\'f3 th\u7875  cho m\'ecnh m\u7897 t l\u7901 i gi\u7843 i th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Simon k\uc0\u7873  s\'e1t \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o h\u7855 n, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Nghe n\'f3i... T\'f4i ch\u7881  l\'e0 nghe n\'f3i th\'f4i nh\'e9, c\'e1i vi\u803  c\u7853 u \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\'ecn Alex \u273 ang s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t: "Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 t\'f4i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\'e1m ch\'edn ph\u7847 n l\'e0 th\u7853 t, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7897 c t\u7915  n\u417 i kh\'e1c c\u7889  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y sao? H\u417 n n\u7919 a \u273 \u7883 a \u273 i\u7875 m bu\u7893 i ti\u7879 c c\u361 ng \u273 \u7893 i t\u7915  n\u417 i ch\'fang ta th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i trong th\'e0nh ph\u7889  qua n\u417 i n\'e0y... D\'f9 sao v\u7883  t\u7899 i nam b\'e1n c\u7847 u l\u7847 n n\'e0y kia v\u7851 n lu\'f4n r\u7845 t \'edt xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f4ng khai l\'f4\u803  m\u259 \u803 t, ai m\'e0 ng\u7901  \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\'faa \uc0\u417 i," Alex \'f4m \u273 \u7847 u r\'ean m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t c\u7853 u trai b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng o\'e1n h\u7853 n v\'ec b\u7883  tr\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7889 i qu\u7843 n l\'fd, "V\u7883  kia c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec m\'e0 ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p ch\u7913 , th\u7871  n\'e0o l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7913 ng th\'fa v\u7899 i bu\u7893 i ti\u7879 c c\u7887 n con c\u7911 a ch\'fang ta? V\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i? Th\u7871  l\'e0 xong, c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u l\'e3o gia h\u7887 a nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\u7847 n n\'e0y ch\u7855 c l\u7841 i ch\u417 i m\u7845 y tr\'f2 h\u7873  c\u361  r\'edch r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Su\uc0\u7925 t, n\'f3i nh\u7887  th\'f4i." Simon nh\'ecn xung quanh, gi\u417  tay ra hi\u7879 u "Ch\u7899  c\'f3 l\'ean ti\u7871 ng" .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n v\u7895  v\u7895  b\u7843  vai c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901  c\u7911 a b\u7841 n m\'ecnh, an \u7911 i: "Th\u7843  l\u7887 ng \u273 i, \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng \u273 \u7841 i nh\'e2n v\u7853 t kia. D\u7921 a theo t\'e1c phong trong l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n, v\u7883  kia lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng c\'f4ng khai l\u7897  di\u7879 n, nhi\u7873 u nh\u7845 t l\'e0 \u7903  trong s\u7843 nh ti\u7871 p m\u7845 y l\'e3o gia h\u7887 a \u273 \u7871 n ch\'e0o h\u7887 i. V\u7883  \u273 \'f3 v\u7899 i ch\'fang ta kh\'f4ng c\'f3 quan h\u7879  g\'ec. Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\'f4i n\'f3i ch\u7913 , l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u7853 u th\u7853 t l\'e0, th\u7871  m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 mang ba nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n, c\'f2n c\'f3 hai c\'e1i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7899 i \u273 \u7871 n t\u7915  ph\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \'f4ng..."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n li\u7871 m li\u7871 m r\u259 ng: "... H\'f4m nay ch\'fang ta s\u7869  t\u7853 n h\u432 \u7903 ng."\cb1 \
