\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n sau khi v\'e0o c\u7917 a li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y Alex v\'e0 Emily \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n khu\'f4n m\u7863 t quen thu\u7897 c n\'e0o, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i b\u432 ng r\u432 \u7907 u \u273 i loanh quanh trong h\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng ti\u7879 c r\u432 \u7907 u n\'e0y c\'f2n l\u7899 n h\u417 n so v\u7899 i t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Sau khi v\'e0o c\u7917 a, \u7903  ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a l\'e0 m\u7897 t s\u7843 nh \u273 \u7841 i y\u7871 n h\u7897 i, \u7903  hai b\'ean s\u7843 nh ch\'ednh c\'f2n c\'f3 b\u7889 n s\u7843 nh b\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong g\'f3c s\uc0\u7843 nh ch\'ednh c\'f3 m\u7897 t d\'e0n nh\u7841 c \u273 ang di\u7877 n t\u7845 u m\u7897 t b\u7843 n nh\u7841 c ch\u7853 m, \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean kh\'e1c th\'ec b\'e0y b\'e0n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\'f3 b\u7891 i b\'e0n \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7891  \u259 n m\u7899 i l\'ean, hoa qu\u7843 , b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t v\'e0 r\u432 \u7907 u. Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng c\'f9ng nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  v\u7867  ngo\'e0i n\u7893 i b\u7853 t \u259 n v\u7853 n \u273 \u7865 p \u273 \u7869  thong th\u7843  \u273 i d\u7841 o trong h\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng \'97\'97 b\u7885 n h\u7885  d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7873 u quen bi\u7871 t nhau. C\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'f3m nam n\u7919  tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i kh\'f4ng ch\'each l\u7879 ch tu\u7893 i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7855 m, b\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  r\'eca ngo\'e0i, chung m\u7897 t ch\u7895  v\u7899 i v\'f2ng giao ti\u7871 p c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac b\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n l\'e0 b\u7843 y gi\u7901  t\u7889 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u7903  h\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng loanh quanh kh\u7855 p n\u417 i nh\'e0m ch\'e1n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n h\u417 n t\'e1m gi\u7901 , ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\u7913  duy nh\u7845 t c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng h\u7845 p d\u7851 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  ch\u7881  c\'f3 b\'e0n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n b\'ean kia, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng ng\u7841 i \u273 i l\u7845 y \u273 \u7891  \u259 n li\'ean t\u7909 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n c\u7847 m ch\'e9n r\u432 \u7907 u kh\'f4ng tr\'ean tay \u273 \u7875  qua m\u7897 t b\'ean tr\'ean b\'e0n, ch\u7881  ch\u7881  s\u7843 nh b\'ean ph\u7843 i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , t\'f4i qua b\'ean kia xem m\u7897 t c\'e1i, ti\u7879 n th\u7875  t\'ecm \u273 \'e1m Alex. C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ti\u7879 c r\u432 \u7907 u n\'e0y \u273 \u7883 nh t\u7893  ch\u7913 c \u273 \u7871 n bao gi\u7901  \u273 \'e2y, l\'fac n\'e0o m\u7899 i v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\'ednh \u273 \u7873 ." C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  c\u7843  \u273 \'eam \u273 \u7873 u th\u7871  n\'e0y ch\u7913 , ch\u7881  l\'e0 t\u7841 o \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n cho m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7847 m r\u432 \u7907 u n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau hay sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, t\'f4i ch\u7901  c\u7853 u \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y, c\'f3 g\'ec th\'ec nh\u7855 n tin li\'ean l\u7841 c." Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 a m\u7855 t nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\u432 ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7845 y ra \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ch\u417 i, d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 nh\u7847 m, c\u7853 u v\u7915 a ch\u417 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 m\u7897 t nam nh\'e2n \u273 i t\u7899 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng b\u7855 t chuy\u7879 n n\'f3i: "Sao l\u7841 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u7903  \u273 \'e2y? Ai \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n hay l\'e0 sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n nh\'ecn qua r\uc0\u7845 t tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i, ch\u7881  t\u7847 m hai b\u7843 y hai t\'e1m. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t th\'e2n ph\u7853 n v\'e0 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i l\u7877  \u273 \u7897  thu \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "T\'f4i l\'e0 sinh vi\'ean AHU, b\u7841 n h\u7885 c cho t\'f4i thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i d\u7851 n t\'f4i t\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y, v\u7851 n c\'f2n l\'e0 sinh vi\'ean... B\u7841 n c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i ch\u417 i, v\u7853 y t\u7889 i nay \u273 i c\'f9ng t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?" Nam nh\'e2n c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 a ra l\u7901 i m\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean chung quy lu\'f4n c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\u7901 i n\'f3i v\'e0 ng\u7919  kh\'ed n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a nam nh\'e2n c\'f3 h\u417 i c\u7893  qu\'e1i, v\'ec v\u7853 y t\u7855 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i t\u7915  ch\u7889 i n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, c\'f3 l\u7869  t\'f4i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n khuya, b\u7841 n t\'f4i s\u7869  \u273 \u432 a t\'f4i c\'f9ng tr\u7903  v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u gi\u7843  v\u7901  l\u7841 i l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ra xem gi\u7901 , g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\'e0o \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i: "Th\u7901 i gian kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7899 m, t\'f4i n\'ean \u273 i t\'ecm b\u7885 n h\u7885  r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i xong thu l\uc0\u7841 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, quay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda Giang \u272 i\u7873 n r\u7901 i \u273 i. N\u7871 u Giang \u272 i\u7873 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  kh\'f4ng t\'ecm th\u7845 y m\'ecnh th\'ec nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  g\u7885 i cho m\'ecnh ho\u7863 c l\'e0 g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n lo l\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7843 n c\u7853 u, ch\u7881  m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\u432 ng c\u7853 u r\u7901 i \u273 i... V\u7873  s\u7899 m m\u7897 t ch\'fat? C\u7853 u trai \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau n\'e0y e l\'e0 v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\u417 i m\'ecnh \u273 \u7871 n r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c n\u417 i n\'e0o r\u7891 i...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7915 a \u273 i v\u7873  h\u432 \u7899 ng kia ch\u432 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai b\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7893  tay, Alex v\u7895  c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7903  ph\'e0o n\'f3i: "T\u7841  \u417 n Ch\'faa, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u361 ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u r\u7891 i. Kevin \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u ta \u273 i t\'ecm c\'e1c c\u7853 u r\u7891 i m\'e0? C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p sao?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y..." Alex l\u7849 m b\u7849 m m\u7897 t c\'e2u, l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, "V\u7853 y tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n lo cho c\u7853 u ta, c\'f3 c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \u7911  r\u7891 i, l\'e1t n\u7919 a \u273 i t\'ecm c\u7853 u ta sau." N\'f3i xong li\u7873 n k\'e9o c\u7853 u \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda m\u7897 t s\u7843 nh b\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7889  g\u7855 ng r\'fat tay m\'ecnh l\u7841 i, t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ra, Alex th\u7871  m\'e0 kh\'ed l\u7921 c r\u7845 t l\u7899 n, tay c\u7853 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  k\'ecm s\u7855 t k\u7865 p, gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a kh\'f4ng ra. May m\'e0 Alex ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\u7853 u v\'f9ng v\u7851 y, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng bu\'f4ng tay c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean xoa xoa c\uc0\u7893  tay tr\'e1i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh: "Sao l\u7841 i n\'f3i c\'f3 t\'f4i l\'e0 \u273 \u7911  r\u7891 i? Ph\u7843 i l\'e0m g\'ec \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "... \uc0\u272 \'e1nh b\'e0i." Alex quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, "B\'e0i poker, bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng? Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t th\'ec b\u7885 n t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7841 y c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Bi\uc0\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c s\u7869  gi\u7889 ng quy t\u7855 c c\u7911 a c\'e1c c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng ch\u7855 c s\u7869  h\u7885 c nhanh th\'f4i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo Alex \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n s\u7843 nh b\'ean, ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng chi\u7871 c s\'f4 pha \u273 \u7887  s\u7853 m h\'ecnh tr\'f2n \u7903  g\'f3c sau c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7915  b\u7885 n h\u7885  ra c\'f2n c\'f3 n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i, Simon, Jody \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  nh\'f3m n\'e0y, nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c c\u361 ng \'edt nhi\u7873 u c\'f3 ch\'fat quen m\u7863 t, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 b\u7841 n b\'e8 th\u432 \u7901 ng qua l\u7841 i v\u7899 i Alex.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n cho Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, b\u7843 o h\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  s\'f4 pha trong s\u7843 nh b\'ean tr\'e1i t\'ecm b\u7885 n h\u7885 , sau \u273 \'f3 ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u h\u7887 i: "Emily \u273 \'e2u? Sao c\'f4 \u7845 y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7903  \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7875  \'fd c\'f4 ta, " Alex tho\u7843 i m\'e1i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i, "Ch\u7855 c c\'f4 ta \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1 quen chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y r\u7891 i, \u273 \u7875  c\'f4 ta t\u7921  \u273 i ch\u417 i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7843 nh b\'ean n\'e0y r\u7845 t y\'ean t\u297 nh, sau khi \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i li\u7873 n ng\u259 n c\'e1ch to\'e0n b\u7897  ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, ti\u7871 ng nh\u7841 c \u7891 n \'e0o c\'f9ng ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n b\'ean ngo\'e0i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7909  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\u7895  nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'e1nh b\'e0i th\u7901 i gian tr\'f4i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t nhanh, sau ba v\'e1n Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ra nh\'ecn, tr\'ean m\'e0n h\'ecnh hi\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 ch\'edn gi\u7901  n\u259 m t\'e1m.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e3 h\u417 n m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i, Kevin sao v\u7851 n ch\u432 a qua \u273 \'e2y, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 b\u7883  m\u7929  n\u7919  n\'e0o m\'ea ho\u7863 c r\u7891 i ch\u7913 ?" C\u7853 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'f9a vui tr\'eau ch\u7885 c, c\u7847 m b\'e0i trong tay \u273 \u7875  l\'ean b\'e0n nh\u7887  tr\u432 \u7899 c s\'f4 pha, "T\'f4i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i t\'ecm c\u7853 u ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i xong \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, \u273 ang l\'fac chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, s\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c th\u7871  nh\u432 ng to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7873 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, ng\u7847 m ch\u7863 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao th\uc0\u7871 ? T\'f4i mu\u7889 n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i t\'ecm Kevin, Simon, l\'e0m phi\u7873 n nh\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'fac n\'e0y l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, kh\'f4ng r\'f5 v\'ec sao b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean theo m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Simon kh\'f4ng h\uc0\u7873  \u273 \u7897 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, ch\u7881  \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3 nh\'ecn c\u7853 u. \u272 \'e8n trong s\u7843 nh r\u7845 t t\u7889 i, n\u7917 a m\u7863 t h\u7855 n \u7849 n trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i, ph\'e1c h\u7885 a m\u7897 t b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\u432 \u7901 i qu\u7927  d\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac n\'e0y ph\'e1t hi\uc0\u7879 n b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng. \'c1nh m\u7855 t c\u7853 u \u273 \u7843 o qua m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, c\'e0ng x\'e1c nh\u7853 n \'97\'97 b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0 c\u7889  \'fd c\u7843 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  con m\'e8o kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd t\u7889 t ch\u7863 n l\u7889 i c\u7911 a con chu\u7897 t nh\u7887  kh\'f4ng n\u417 i \u273 \u7875  tr\u7889 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Alex, c\u7893  h\u7885 ng b\u7895 ng h\u417 i \u273 \u7897 ng, gi\u7843  b\u7897  tho\u7843 i m\'e1i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "... \u272 ang ch\u417 i tr\'f2 g\'ec sao? Hay l\'e0 tr\'f2 \u273 \'f9a g\'ec m\'e0 t\'f4i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex c\'fai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u li\u7871 c nh\'ecn \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891  tr\'ean c\u7893  tay tr\'e1i, c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u: "Jerry, nh\u7901  c\'f3 c\u7853 u nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  t\'f4i m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c theo \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\u361 ng nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i di \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, \u273 \'e3 l\u7841 i qua ba ph\'fat, b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  l\u7867  m\u7897 t ph\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t c\'e2u "\u272 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  r\u7891 i" c\u7911 a Alex gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\'eca kh\'f3a m\u7903  ch\u7889 t, sau \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng ai n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng to\'e0n b\u7897  s\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i d\'f9ng m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i \'e1nh m\u7855 t n\'f3ng b\u7887 ng d\u7883  th\u432 \u7901 ng g\u7855 t gao nh\'ecn c\u7853 u b\u7883  v\'e2y \u7903  ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a. Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'f9ng d\u432  quang li\u7871 c v\u7873  ph\'eda hai ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  t\'ean, th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t m\'e0n c\u7921 c k\u7923  kinh s\u7907 \'97\'97 trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i, huy\u7871 t s\u7855 c tr\'ean m\u7863 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  to\'e0n b\u7897  r\'fat \u273 i, bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh m\'e0u xanh tr\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 sinh kh\'ed, c\'e0ng th\'eam \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  l\'e0 c\'f3 hai chi\u7871 c r\u259 ng nanh d\'e0i v\u432 \u417 n ra t\u7915  trong m\'f4i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  d\u7885 a \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i tim g\u7847 n nh\u432  mu\u7889 n ng\u7915 ng \u273 \u7853 p, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng thay \u273 \u7893 i t\u7847 m m\u7855 t, c\u361 ng may, Alex v\'e0 Simon v\u7851 n l\'e0 b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u l\'e0n da h\'ecnh nh\u432  tr\u7903  n\'ean t\'e1i nh\u7907 t h\u417 n so v\u7899 i ng\'e0y th\u432 \u7901 ng\'97\'97 \u273 i\u7873 u n\'e0y c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 do t\'e1c d\u7909 ng t\'e2m l\'fd g\'e2y ra, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 do hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  \'e1nh s\'e1ng t\u7841 o th\'e0nh \u7843 o gi\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng kh\'ed b\uc0\u7889 n ph\'eda tr\u7903  n\'ean c\u7921 c k\u7923  y\'ean t\u297 nh. D\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  ngay c\u7843  ti\u7871 ng tim \u273 \u7853 p c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ng\u7915 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i s\u7907 , kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i s\u7907 , ch\u7855 c l\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u7889  \'fd t\u7841 o b\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed qu\u7927  d\u7883  \u273 \u7875  d\u7885 a m\'ecnh, mu\u7889 n th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\u7841 ng m\'ecnh b\u7883  d\u7885 a s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7875 u ra qu\u7847 n m\u7845 t m\u7863 t th\'f4i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang c\u7889  g\u7855 ng an \u7911 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u7903  trong kh\'f4ng kh\'ed y\'ean t\u297 nh m\'e0 b\'ed hi\u7875 m n\'e0y \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  \'97\'97 c\u7853 u \'e2m th\u7847 m x\'ea d\u7883 ch v\u7873  ph\'eda Alex, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\u7897 t l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\uc0\u7887 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng\'97\'97 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c, m\'e0 l\'e0 ngay t\u7915  l\'fac b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u, ti\u7871 ng tim \u273 \u7853 p c\u7911 a t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ng\u7915 ng. Gi\u7901  n\'e0y kh\u7855 c n\'e0y, \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng tim \u273 \u7853 p c\u7911 a m\u7897 t m\'ecnh m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, tr\u7915  m\'ecnh ra, b\u7885 n h\u7885  th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7891 ng t\u7917  Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t co l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Simon d\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\u7921 c k\u7923  h\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7909  b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\u7853 u s\u7907  h\'e3i khi th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng, h\'e9 mi\u7879 ng n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i. H\u7855 n h\'e0i l\'f2ng li\u7871 m r\u259 ng \'97\'97 d\'e0i v\'e0 s\u7855 c b\'e9n, r\u259 ng nanh l\'f3e h\'e0n quang.\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex d\'f9ng ng\uc0\u7919  \u273 i\u7879 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\u7845 n an an \u7911 i: "Y\'ean t\'e2m, Jerry, \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907 , s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 au l\u7855 m \u273 \'e2u, b\u7885 n t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u. N\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\u7853 u c\'f2n s\u7869  th\'edch c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i c\u361 ng r\u7845 t h\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7909  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  Emily."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7841 i n\'e3o Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhanh ch\'f3ng x\u7917  l\'fd m\u7845 y ch\u7919  m\u7845 u ch\u7889 t nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, "\u272 au" "Nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i" "H\'fat m\'e1u" ... B\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0... qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t...?\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1p \'e1n n\'e0y ho\'e0n to\'e0n v\u432 \u7907 t ra kh\u7887 i t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ngc\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i th\u7871  gi\u7899 i th\u7853 t, trong l\'fac nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \'e3 ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  h\u7891 i l\'e2u kh\'f4ng cho c\u7853 u th\'eam th\u7901 i gian ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng n\u7919 a, d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  ch\u7881  d\u7851 n c\u7911 a Alex t\u7915 ng ch\'fat m\u7897 t \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n c\u7853 u, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n thu nh\u7887  v\'f2ng v\'e2y.\cb1 \
