\cf2 \cb3 Sau khi c\'e1nh c\uc0\u7917 a \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, Jody c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7845 t b\'ecnh tr\u7915 ng v\u7873  h\u432 \u7899 ng t\'e2y: "\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 ai? V\'ec sao l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  \'f4ng ta mang Jerry \u273 i? Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean sao? Ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p, m\'f9i m\'e1u c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, h\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o c\u7905  n\'e0o..."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 ta nh\uc0\u432  \u273 ang h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng m\'f9i v\u7883  kia, gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t m\u361 i: "Th\u7853 t v\u7845 t v\u7843  m\u7899 i c\'f3 c\u417  h\u7897 i h\'f4m nay, h\u7855 n nh\u7853 n thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i th\u7883 nh y\u7871 n m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i theo Alex \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i n\'e0y, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i h\'f4m nay h\u7855 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 con m\u7891 i c\u7911 a ch\'fang ta, ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'f9y \'fd x\u7917  tr\'ed h\u7855 n. Th\u7871  m\'e0 m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i th\u7843  h\u7855 n \u273 i v\u7899 i m\u7897 t k\u7867  l\u7841 ? Trong t\u7897 c r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 quy \u273 \u7883 nh, con m\u7891 i ai mang \u273 \u7871 n th\'ec thu\u7897 c v\u7873  k\u7867  \u273 \'f3, kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 t\u432  c\'e1ch \u273 o\u7841 t con m\u7891 i c\u7911 a ch\'fang ta, \u273 \'fang ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 Emmer Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng." Alex l\'ean ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  m\u7897 t c\'e2u n\'f3i \u273 \'e3 khi\u7871 n cho Jody tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p t\u7855 t \'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Emmer Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng... ?" C\'f4 ta v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng l\u7863 p l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng sai, v\uc0\u7915 a r\u7891 i v\u7883  kia ch\'ednh l\'e0 qu\u7843 n gia c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 ." Simon n\'f3i ti\u7871 p, "T\u7841  \u417 n Ch\'faa, c\'f4 \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n g\'ec ngu xu\u7849 n ch\u7885 c \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng Jerry r\u417 i v\'e0o tay h\u7855 n th\u7853 t qu\'e1 \u273 \'e1ng ti\u7871 c.." M\u7897 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'e1c nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i, l\u7841 i b\u7883  \'e1nh m\u7855 t \'e2m hi\u7875 m c\u7911 a Simon l\'e0m s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c ng\u7853 m mi\u7879 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i ti\u7871 p n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t "\u272 \'e1ng ti\u7871 c" trong l\u7901 i t\'ean kia l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec \'97\'97m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t b\'ed m\u7853 t c\'f4ng khai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Emmer Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 t\'ednh khi\u7871 t ph\'edch k\'ec l\u7841 , h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bao gi\u7901  tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p h\'fat m\'e1u t\u7915  c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 s\u7869  \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7847 u \u273 \u7893  m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i v\'e0o ly th\u7911 y tinh r\u7891 i m\u7899 i u\u7889 ng. Nh\u432 ng to\'e0n b\u7897  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0m nh\u432  v\u7853 y s\u7869  khi\u7871 n huy\u234 \u769 t di\u803 ch t\u432 \u417 i ngon m\u7845 t \u273 i bao nhi\'eau t\u432  v\u7883 , qu\u7843  th\u7921 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u259 n b\'edt-t\u7871 t ch\'edn, m\'f9i v\u7883  ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng c\'f2n, trong m\u7855 t b\u7885 n h\u7855 n, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng n\u7855 m gi\u7919  quy\u7873 n th\u7871  v\'e0 t\'e0i nguy\'ean v\'f4 t\u7853 n, v\u7889 n m\u7895 i ng\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng xa x\u7881  h\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7909  m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p t\u7915  c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 l\u7841 i l\'e0m nh\u432  th\u7871  qu\u7843  th\u7921 c ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\u7921 c k\'ec l\'e3ng ph\'ed.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n c\'f3 tin t\u7913 c nho nh\u7887  n\'f3i Emmer Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng g\u7847 n tr\u259 m n\u259 m nay \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t \'edt h\u7845 p thu m\'e1u, nghe n\'f3i h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7883  gi\'e1c nh\u432  nh\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'e1c, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i h\u7913 ng th\'fa v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c n\u7871 m th\u7917  nhi\u7873 u lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \'97\'97 \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean \u273 \'e2y ch\u7881  l\'e0 tin v\u7883 t kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o kh\u7843 o ch\u7913 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c cho l\'e0 th\'e2\u803 t. D\'f9 sao s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7847 n nh\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n m\'e1u \u273 \u7875  duy tr\'ec, n\u7871 u nh\u432  Emmer Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  nh\u432  trong l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n, \u273 \'e3 hai tr\u259 m ba tr\u259 m n\u259 m kh\'f4ng h\'fat m\'e1u, nh\u432  v\u7853 y s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n m\u7845 y, \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng c\u361 ng ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  b\u7883  th\'e1ch th\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng s\u7921  th\u7853 t l\'e0 \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3i s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh gi\u7843 m xu\u7889 ng, cho \u273 \u7871 n nay th\u7853 m ch\'ed to\'e0n b\u7897  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7845 y ai c\'f3 gan nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n t\'ean h\u7855 n. R\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i c\u259 n b\u7843 n ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chi\'eam ng\u432 \u7905 ng h\u7855 n, nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i ch\u7883 u \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7911 a th\u7871  h\u7879  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y k\'ednh s\u7907  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i v\u7883  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i ch\uc0\u7881  hy v\u7885 ng... Jerry s\u7869  bi\u7871 t \u273 i\u7873 u th\u7913 c th\u7901 i m\'e0 l\'e0m vui l\'f2ng v\u7883  \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia, \u273 \u7915 ng g\'e2y phi\u7873 n to\'e1i g\'ec cho ch\'fang ta, v\u7873  sau chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y coi nh\u432  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng x\u7843 y ra, l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c." Simon kh\u7869  n\'f3i. H\u7855 n r\u7845 t lo l\u7855 ng thanh ni\'ean l\u7895  m\'e3ng kia \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, v\u7899 i th\u7883 nh y\u7871 n m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i, v\u7899 i Emmer Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t g\'ec, s\u7869  ch\u7885 c ra r\u7855 c r\u7889 i n\'e0o \u273 \'f3, l\u7841 i g\'e2y h\u7885 a cho b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7843 nh b\'ean nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i r\u417 i v\'e0o tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n l\'e0 Alex ph\'e1 v\u7905  im l\u7863 ng: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, \u273 \u7915 ng ngh\u297  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y n\u7919 a, ch\'fang ta c\u361 ng n\'ean \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i t\'ecm \u273 \u7891  \u259 n th\'f4i. Ch\'fang ta c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t Kevin ho\'e0n to\'e0n t\u432 \u417 i m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i sao? \u272 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7875  k\u7867  kh\'e1c \u273 o\u7841 t tr\u432 \u7899 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 \'fd ni\u7879 m duy nh\u7845 t trong \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\'ednh l\'e0 r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i s\u7843 nh b\'ean. B\u7845 t k\u7875  th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 n\'f3i, c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i s\u7843 nh b\'ean n\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i t\'ednh ti\u7871 p, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng n\'e0o t\u7879  h\u417 n so v\u7899 i b\u7883  s\'e1u con qu\'e1i v\u7853 t v\'e2y l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\u7895 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7917 a s\u7843 nh b\'ean ph\'eda sau kh\'e9p l\u7841 i, trong l\'f2ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c hi\u7879 n l\'ean m\u7897 t tia hy v\u7885 ng s\u7889 ng s\'f3t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng t\'f3c x\'e1m r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u432  nh\'ecn th\u7845 u \'fd ngh\u297  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, th\u7843 n nhi\'ean m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "Ta khuy\'ean ng\'e0i t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t th\'e0nh th\u7853 t c\'f9ng ta \u273 i g\u7863 p \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , kh\'f4ng n\'ean \'f4m \'fd ni\u7879 m may m\u7855 n kh\'e1c trong \u273 \u7847 u. Ng\'e0i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 t con ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ng\'e0i b\'e2y gi\u7901  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh s\u7869  nh\u7853 n h\u7853 u qu\u7843  g\'ec \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'edu nh\'edu m\'e0y, nh\uc0\u432 ng tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y \u273 \'fang. Tuy r\u7857 ng hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i s\uc0\u7843 nh b\'ean l\'e0 m\u7897 t h\'e0nh lang tr\u7889 ng tr\u7843 i, l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i c\'f9ng Alex v\'e0o s\u7843 nh b\'ean, n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7845 y nh\'f3m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng t\'fam t\u7909 m n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, v\u7853 y m\'e0 gi\u7901  kh\u7855 c n\'e0y trong h\'e0nh lang tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a l\u7899 n c\u7911 a h\'e0nh lang th\'f4ng v\u7899 i ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch ch\'ednh c\u361 ng kh\'e9p ch\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch ch\'ednh, " Ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng t\'f3c x\'e1m thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch, "Ch\u7881  c\'f3 con m\u7891 i b\u7883  mang \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n chia s\u7867  v\u7899 i k\u7867  kh\'e1c m\u7899 i b\u7883  gi\u7845 u trong s\u7843 nh m\u7897 t m\'ecnh h\u432 \u7903 ng d\u7909 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7919  kh\'ed ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng r\u7845 t b\'ecnh th\u7843 n, nh\u432 ng m\u7895 i l\u7901 i ra t\u7915  mi\u7879 ng h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7909 ng v\'e0o th\u7847 n kinh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, m\u7895 i c\'e2u n\'f3i \u273 \u7873 u t\u7887  r\'f5 v\u7899 i c\u7853 u r\u7857 ng n\u417 i n\'e0y, y\u7871 n h\u7897 i n\'e0y so v\u7899 i t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\'f2n b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng h\u417 n, \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  h\u417 n, kh\'f3 \u273 \'e0o tho\'e1t h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n d\u7851 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915  c\u7847 u thang cu\u7889 i h\'e0nh lang \u273 i l\'ean l\u7847 u hai, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c b\u7853 c thang \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean, do d\u7921  m\'e0 b\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng ra b\u432 \u7899 c. Trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u r\u7845 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng, sau khi l\'ean l\u7847 u r\u7891 i, mu\u7889 n ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 n s\u7869  ch\u7881  c\'e0ng kh\'f3 h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 t\uc0\u7915  l\'fac theo ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng \u273 i ra c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 l\u7863 ng l\u7869  x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh, v\u7915 a qua m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901 , t\'edn hi\u7879 u \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  ch\u7863 n to\'e0n b\u7897 , hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7845 t k\u7923  c\'e1ch n\'e0o li\'ean l\u7841 c tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p v\u7899 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng t\'ednh t\'ecnh c\u361 ng d\u7877  ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7913 ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7901  c\u7853 u: "Xin l\u7895 i ti\'ean sinh. Nh\u432 ng th\u7913  cho t\'f4i n\'f3i th\u7859 ng, ng\'e0i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n n\'e0o kh\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang v\u7853 y, \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau k\u7867  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  \u273 i c\'f9ng h\u7855 n, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n n\'e0o kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng t\'f3c x\'e1m d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'e0ng nh\'ecn c\'e0ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y quen m\u7855 t, sau \u273 \'f3 gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh nh\u7899  ra m\'ecnh t\u7915 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u7903  ti\u7879 m hamburger g\u7847 n k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1. B\u7903 i v\'ec l\'fac \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u259 n m\u7863 c qu\'e1 kh\'f4ng \u259 n nh\u7853 p v\u7899 i ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh xung quanh, d\'f9 \u273 \'e3 qua h\u417 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n gi\u7919  \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng nh\u432  c\u361  v\u7899 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 y l\'e0... H\u7855 n mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n m\'ecnh \u273 i g\u7863 p ch\u7911  nh\'e2n b\'e0n tay kia?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd ngh\uc0\u297  n\'e0y \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n trong \u273 \u7847 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\'f4 h\u7845 p tr\'ec tr\u7879 , kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7899  l\u7841 i gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, n\u7895  l\u7921 c t\u7921  n\'f3i v\u7899 i m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng n\'ean suy ngh\u297  lung tung, tuy r\u7857 ng m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \'eam nay \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng v\u432 \u7907 t xa ph\u7841 m vi kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  c\u7911 a m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\u432 ng hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i duy tr\'ec \u273 \u7911  tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh v\'e0 t\u7881 nh t\'e1o m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  ngh\u297  c\'e1ch \u273 \u432 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ki\uc0\u7871 n tr\'fac b\'ean trong l\'e0 s\'e2n thi\u7871 t k\u7871  m\u7903 , ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh l\u7847 u m\u7897 t kh\'f4ng d\u7877  ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7847 u tr\'ean, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  h\'e0nh lang l\u7847 u tr\'ean l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7921 a g\'f3c quan th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c to\'e0n b\u7897  h\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7847 u d\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng tr\'ean c\u7847 u thang xo\u7855 n \u7889 c l\u7847 u hai, Tr\'ec Di\'ean thu\u7853 n m\u7855 t li\u7871 c v\u7873  ph\'eda y\u7871 n h\u7897 i \u273 \'e8n \u273 u\u7889 c s\'e1ng tr\u432 ng trong ph\'f2ng, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f3 m\'e0 d\u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n \'97\'97 qu\'e1i v\u7853 t c\'f3 b\u7873  ngo\'e0i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i l\u7841 i m\u7885 c ra r\u259 ng nanh \u273 ang \u273 \'e8 nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i \u7903  g\'f3c t\u432 \u7901 ng, h\'e0m r\u259 ng b\'e9n nh\u7885 n trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t xuy\'ean th\u7911 ng l\'e0n da m\u7873 m m\u7841 i, x\'e2m nh\u7853 p c\u7847 n c\u7893 ... C\'f3 qu\'e1i v\u7853 t qu\'e1 m\u7913 c n\'f4n n\'f3ng, l\'fac \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o qu\'e1 d\'f9ng s\u7913 c khi\u7871 n m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i phun ra, r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng \'e1o s\u417 mi ho\u7863 c v\'e1y l\u7909 a m\u7887 ng tr\u7855 ng nh\u432  tuy\u7871 t... C\'f3 nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i s\u7855 c m\u7863 t ho\u7843 ng s\u7907 , run r\u7849 y tr\u7889 n ra khu r\'eca ngo\'e0i, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \'eam nay ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t g\'ec; m\'e0 c\'f3 nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i c\u361 ng r\u7845 t b\'ecnh th\u7843 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng c\'e2u l\u7845 y r\u259 ng nanh c\u7911 a qu\'e1i v\u7853 t tr\'ean qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\'f2n d\'ednh m\'e1u. M\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ngo\u7841 i l\u7879 , t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i l\'fac b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u v\u7867  m\u7863 t \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n hay m\'ea say, bi\u7875 u l\u7897  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7845 t h\u7891 n l\u7841 c ph\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i c\'e2u n\'f3i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c Alex \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i\'97\'97 "Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7875  \'fd c\'f4 ta, ch\u7855 c c\'f4 ta \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1 quen chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y r\u7891 i, \u273 \u7875  c\'f4 ta t\u7921  \u273 i ch\u417 i \u273 i " .\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean n\'f3i v\uc0\u7853 y l\'e0 v\'ec Emily l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m bi\u7871 t h\'f4m nay l\'e0 n\u417 i n\'e0o d\u7841 ng g\'ec, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f4 ta \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e1m Alex l\'e0 qu\'e1i v\u7853 t nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, h\'f4m nay l\'e0 t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n theo t\u7899 i?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 v\'ec sao? L\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875 ? ! C\'f4 ta m\u7845 t tr\'ed \u273 i\'ean r\u7891 i hay sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn s\uc0\u417  qua, m\u7897 t n\u7917 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f9i m\'e1u tanh lan kh\uc0\u7855 p to\'e0n b\u7897  h\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng, h\'f3a ra ch\u7911  \u273 \u7873  y\u7871 n h\u7897 i n\'e0y l\'e0 nh\u432  v\u7853 y n\'e0y, th\u7901 i gian v\u7915 a \u273 \u7871 n, n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y li\u7873 n bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh ti\u7879 c \u259 n u\u7889 ng hoan vui c\u7911 a qu\'e1i v\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng t\'f3c x\'e1m \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh th\'fac gi\u7909 c: "B\u7845 t lu\u7853 n ng\'e0i mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean m\u7901 i theo ta \u273 i g\u7863 p \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 . \u272 \u432 a ng\'e0i \u273 \u7871 n l\'e0 nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  c\u7911 a ta." Tr\'ean th\u7921 c t\u7871  h\u7855 n r\u7845 t s\u7907  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  b\u7903 i v\'ec h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7853 m tr\u7877  qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u th\u7901 i gian m\'e0 \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f4ng ki\'ean nh\u7851 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f3 kh\uc0\u259 n di chuy\u7875 n b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'ean ti\u7871 ng x\'e1c nh\u7853 n: "... B\u7885 n h\u7885 , ho\u7863 c l\'e0 n\'f3i c\'e1c \'f4ng, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec?" M\'e0 c\'e0ng v\'f4 l\'fd h\u417 n ch\'ednh l\'e0, l\'fac n\'e0y v\u7851 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng t\'f3c x\'e1m kia khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \'e1ng tin c\u7853 y h\u417 n, ch\u7881  l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec h\'ecnh nh\u432  \'f4ng ta r\u7845 t c\'f3 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  c\u7909 c di\u7879 n, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  b\u7883  m\'f9i m\'e1u \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng m\'e0 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\'e1i v\u7853 t nh\u432  b\u7885 n Alex.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng, mang theo c\u7853 u \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n l\u7847 u ba, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i phun ra m\u7897 t t\u7915 : "Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e2y ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  so v\u417 \u769 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u417 \u768 ng c\'f2n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u417 \u768 ng h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Suy \uc0\u273 o\'e1n l\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\'e1c nh\u7853 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 l\u7921 c nh\u7855 m hai m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn xem b\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 ngu xu\u7849 n kh\'f4ng ch\'fat c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 em m\'ecnh v\'e0 b\u7841 n b\'e8 d\u7851 n v\'e0o t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh si\'eau th\u7921 c nguy hi\u7875 m nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a m\u7897 t c\u259 n ph\'f2ng \u7903  ph\'eda trong c\'f9ng l\u7847 u ba. Tr\'ean tay n\u7855 m c\'e1nh c\u7917 a g\u7895  v\u7855 t m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c kh\u259 n l\u7909 a m\'e0u \u273 en b\u7855 t m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Xin l\uc0\u7895 i, xin ng\'e0i nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t ph\u7889 i h\u7907 p m\u7897 t ch\'fat." Ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng n\'f3i, \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c nhanh ch\'f3ng l\u7845 y kh\u259 n l\u7909 a xu\u7889 ng, c\u7847 m n\'f3 b\u7883 t l\'ean m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7847 m nh\'ecn l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\'e2m v\'e0o b\'f3ng t\u7889 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t m\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh h\u432 \u7899 ng, nh\u7919 ng gi\'e1c quan kh\'e1c l\'fac n\'e0y l\u7841 i tr\u7903  n\'ean nh\u7841 y c\u7843 m h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a ba ti\u7871 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 quay v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh ch\u7881  th\u7883  n\'f3i: "M\u7901 i ng\'e0i v\'e0o."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean do d\uc0\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  b\u7883  v\u432 \u7899 ng \'97\'97 c\'e1nh c\u7917 a kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7915  khi n\'e0o \u273 \'e3 im h\u417 i l\u7863 ng ti\u7871 ng m\u7903  ra. Ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng t\'f3c x\'e1m kh\'f4ng c\'f9ng \u273 i t\u7899 i, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean l\'e0 ch\u7881  \u273 \u7875  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh m\'ecnh \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\'ean trong th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 ang \u273 \u7907 i ch\u7901  m\'ecnh, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  v\u432 \u417 n tay, l\u7847 n m\'f2 ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng ph\uc0\u7911  th\u7843 m d\'e0y, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n m\u7873 m m\u7873 m, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Ngay sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng "c\u7841 ch", c\u7917 a g\u7895  sau l\u432 ng kh\'e9p l\u7841 i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f3a l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean sinh ra s\u7907  h\'e3i, \u273 \u7913 ng nguy\'ean t\u7841 i ch\u7895 , kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean l\'e0m g\'ec. C\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\u7883  l\u7921 c b\u7883  l\u7845 y \u273 i l\'e0m n\u7895 i s\u7907  v\'e0 s\u7921  hoang mang c\'e0ng t\u259 ng th\'eam.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\'e2ng tay tr\'e1i do d\u7921  \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean kh\u259 n l\u7909 a tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t\'97\'97 c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n th\'e1o n\'f3 xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7875  th\u7845 y r\'f5 t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i; l\u7841 i s\u7907  m\u7897 t c\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng n\'e0y s\u7869  l\'e0m ch\u7911  nh\'e2n k\u7923  qu\'e1i n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7869  t\u7921  r\u432 \u7899 c l\u7845 y phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n thi\u7871 t \'97\'97 tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng hi\u7875 u t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  c\'e0ng t\u7879  h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'fap c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 a ra l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n. Ch\u7911  nh\'e2n c\u259 n ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o \u273 \'e3 im \u7855 ng \u273 i t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay h\u7919 u l\u7921 c \u273 \'e8 l\'ean tay tr\'e1i \u273 ang \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean kh\u259 n l\u7909 a c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0n tay n\'e0y l\uc0\u7841 nh bu\u7889 t, thon d\'e0i, kh\u7899 p x\u432 \u417 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  trong gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Y\uc0\u7871 t h\u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chuy\u7875 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7911  nh\'e2n b\'e0n tay c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n m\'ecnh, h\u417 i th\u7903  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o c\u7911 a h\u7855 n kh\u7869  l\u432 \u7899 t tr\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'e1ch m\'ecnh r\u7845 t g\u7847 n \'97\'97 c\'f3 l\u7869  ch\u7881  thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a s\u7869  d\'e1n v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean nghi\'eang m\u7863 t sang ph\u7843 i, kh\'f4ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c theo \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c n\'e0y, ph\u7847 n tr\'e1i c\u7893  m\'ecnh l\u7841 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\u7897  ra d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7855 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\'fai th\u7845 p ng\u432 \u7901 i xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, h\u417 i th\u7903  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o kia t\u7915  tr\'ean cao tr\u432 \u417 \u803 t xu\u7889 ng c\u7893  tr\'e1i c\u7853 u\'97\'97 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\'e0n da tr\u7847 n tr\u7909 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i man m\'e1t, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u432 \u7899 t l\u7841 nh l\u432 \u7899 t qua ph\'eda tr\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0, l\'e0 \uc0\u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 ang li\u7871 m. \'dd ngh\u297  n\'e0y v\u7915 a l\u432 \u7899 t qua trong \u273 \u7847 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i c\u259 ng c\u7913 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t d\'f9ng tay tr\'e1i \u273 \'e8 ch\u7863 t vai ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u, tay ph\u7843 i v\u7889 n d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  ng\u259 n c\u7843 n \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c th\'e1o kh\u259 n l\u7909 a gi\u7901  m\u432 \u7901 i ng\'f3n \u273 an xen v\u7899 i tay tr\'e1i c\u7853 u. Ch\u7881  l\'e0 hai \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\u417 i xu\u7845 t l\u7921 c, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i k\u7873  s\'e1t v\'e0o v\u7899 i nhau, m\u7897 t kh\u7855 c ti\u7871 p theo Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 v\u7853 t c\u7913 ng s\u7855 c nh\u7885 n ch\u7889 ng tr\'ean n\u417 i b\u7883  li\u7871 m qua kia, l\'e0 r\u259 ng nanh c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng... C\u7853 u c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, trong ch\u7899 p m\u7855 t c\u7893  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  v\u7853 t s\u7855 c nh\u7885 n \u273 \'e2m th\u7911 ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  n\u7893 i ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng k\'eau \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n, \u273 \u432 a tay \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7893  hung th\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i c\u417  th\u7875 , \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c k\u7923  di\u7879 u kh\'f3 n\'f3i l\'ean l\u7901 i\'97\'97 c\u7853 u nh\u432  bay l\'ean kh\'f4ng trung, \'fd th\u7913 c tr\u7903  n\'ean tr\'f4i n\u7893 i, th\'e2n th\u7875  r\u7891 i l\u7841 i n\'f3ng l\'ean nh\u432  nh\u361 n ra, hai \u273 \'f9i v\u7899 i hai ch\'e2n g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  n\u7893 i s\u7913 c n\u7863 ng c\u417  th\u7875 , c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  treo tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, d\u7921 a v\'e0o \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \u7913 ng y\'ean. C\u7853 u v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, trong mi\u7879 ng ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng r\'ean r\u7881  r\u7845 t nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh h\'fat m\'e1u c\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  ch\u7881  trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t, l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  d\'e0i d\u7857 ng d\u7863 c, th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi r\u259 ng nh\u7885 n c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\'fat ra t\u7915  c\u7893  m\'ecnh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c \'fd th\u7913 c. C\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u417  h\u7891  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng d\'f9ng m\'f4i l\u432 \u7905 i vu\u7889 t ve n\u417 i c\u7847 n c\u7893  b\u7883  c\u7855 n, c\u361 ng nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng d\'f9ng l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m \u273 i mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng v\'e0 d\u7845 u r\u259 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t k\u7923  di\u7879 u, t\u7841 i th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\'fat ra \u273 \'f3, m\'e1u li\u7873 n ng\u7915 ng tu\'f4n, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 kh\'e9p l\u7841 i trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\'e0i c\u7921 c k\u7923  *th\u7887 a m\'e3n.\cb1 \
