\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Sau m\uc0\u7897 t l\'e1t, b\'e0n tay \u273 \'e8 l\u7841 i vai c\u7853 u c\'f9ng b\'e0n tay giam tay tr\'e1i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7891 ng lo\u7841 t th\u7843  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\'edch \u7913 ng k\u7883 p, sau khi s\u7921 c t\u7881 nh m\u7899 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng bu\'f4ng tay \u273 ang \'f4m c\u7893  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, lui v\u7873  sau m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c duy tr\'ec \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng co qu\u7855 p tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t v\'ec tay ch\'e2n v\'f4 l\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u432 \u417 i \u273 i \u273 i, s\u7869  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u417 i r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i." Thanh \'e2m c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u7921 c k\u7923  l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau m\'e0 t\u7921 a nh\u432  c\'e1ch th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng xa x\'f4i tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p vang l\'ean trong \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 h\'ecnh c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y thanh \'e2m v\'e0 ng\u7919  kh\'ed h\u417 i quen, nh\u432 ng ngay sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c d\u7913 t b\u7887  \'fd ngh\u297  n\'e0y, d\'f9 sao c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng quen bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t v\u7883 ... Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  r\u7845 t c\'f3 \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883  nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y m\'e0 h\u417 i ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \'97\'97 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 mu\u7889 n th\u7843  m\'ecnh \u273 i? H\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u m\'ecnh, \u273 \'e3 h\'e0i l\'f2ng, v\u7853 y n\'ean th\u7843  cho m\'ecnh \u273 i?\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  gi\u7889 ng \u273 ang n\'f3i gi\u7905 n hay tr\'eau \u273 \'f9a m\'ecnh. B\u7903 i v\'ec m\u7863 c d\'f9 l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, c\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o nh\u7919 ng tin t\u7913 c \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t m\'e0 ph\'e1n \u273 o\'e1n, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u r\u7845 t c\'f3 quy\u7873 n th\u7871 , h\u417 n n\u7919 a \u273 ang n\u7855 m gi\u7919  to\'e0n b\u7897  \u432 u th\u7871  c\u7909 c di\u7879 n l\'fac n\'e0y. H\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'f9y \'fd b\'e0i b\u7889  m\'ecnh m\'e0 m\'ecnh c\u259 n b\u7843 n v\'f4 l\u7921 c ph\u7843 n kh\'e1ng, cho n\'ean \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n n\'f3i d\u7889 i hay l\u7915 a g\u7841 t m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0y t\u7889 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng k\u7871 t qu\u7843  Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy \u273 o\'e1n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, d\'f9 sao v\u7915 a r\u7891 i tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\'ecnh nh\u432  r\u7845 t kh\u7855 c ch\u7871 , c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sinh ra c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 e v\'ec m\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u m\'e1u. Nh\'ecn l\u7841 i cho \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901 , chuy\u7871 n \u273 i n\'e0y c\u361 ng ch\u432 a g\'e2y ra t\u7893 n h\u7841 i g\'ec t\u7879  h\u417 n cho c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fd tr\'ed Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\uc0\u7871 t l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u n\'ean nghe l\u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3i, th\u7915 a d\u7883 p tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac h\u7855 n ch\u432 a thay \u273 \u7893 i ch\u7911  \'fd th\'ec h\'e3y im l\u7863 ng m\'e0 mau ch\'f3ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, sau khi r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i th\'ec ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ngh\u297  c\'e1ch t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i c\u7913 u Giang \u272 i\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng hi\u7879 n l\'ean h\'ecnh \u7843 nh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y trong ph\'f2ng y\u7871 n h\u7897 i l\'fac n\'e3y, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i th\'eam n\u7919 a, c\u7853 u s\u7907  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p c\u7913 u Giang \u272 i\u7873 n v\u7873 , c\u7853 u s\u7907  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean g\u7863 p \u7903  n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y b\u7903 i v\'ec c\'f9ng m\'ecnh tham gia m\u7897 t ti\u7879 c r\u432 \u7907 u m\'e0 l\u7841 i ch\u7871 t d\u432 \u7899 i r\u259 ng nanh qu\'e1i v\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean gi\uc0\u7901  kh\u7855 c n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n m\u7897 t quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7921 c k\u7923  m\u7841 o hi\u7875 m \'97\'97 n\u7871 u nh\u432  c\u7853 u kh\'f4n kh\'e9o h\u417 n, hi\u7875 u bi\u7871 t h\u417 n, n\u7871 u c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng v\'ec qu\'e1 ng\'e2y th\u417  m\'e0 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t s\u7907  h\'e3i nh\u432  th\u7871 , c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u361 ng kh\'ed m\'e0 m\u7841 o hi\u7875 m h\u7841  quy\u7871 t t\'e2m li\u7873 u l\u297 nh \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  \u273 \'f3, do d\u7921 , d\'f9ng gi\u7885 ng th\'e0nh kh\u7849 n h\u7871 t m\u7913 c c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 a ra th\u7881 nh c\u7847 u v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t v\u7915 a m\u7899 i h\'fat m\'e1u m\'ecnh: "C\u7843 m \u417 n ng\'e0i, nh\u432 ng m\'e0... t\'f4i \u273 i c\'f9ng m\u7897 t b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y, t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7851 n c\u7853 u ta c\'f9ng r\u7901 i \u273 i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'f4ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u432 a ra \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i, trong ph\'f2ng nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i r\u417 i v\'e0o tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\'e1t sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i l\u7841 i nghe th\u7845 y trong \u273 \u7847 u m\'ecnh c\'f3 m\u7897 t thanh \'e2m m\u7901  \u7843 o: "Ng\u432 \u417 i l\'e0 con m\u7891 i nh\u7853 n thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i \u273 en, ta l\'e0 kh\'e1ch \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng l\u7901 i m\u7901 i m\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n, d\u7921 a theo quy t\u7855 c \u273 \'eam nay ta c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m b\u7845 t c\u7913  chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u417 i. Nh\u432 ng ta ch\u7881  l\u7845 y \u273 i \'edt huy\u234 \u769 t di\u803 ch c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i r\u7891 i \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, b\'e2y gi\u7901  ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f2n mu\u7889 n l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng nh\'e2n t\u7915  c\u7911 a ta th\u7881 nh c\u7847 u mang \u273 i con m\u7891 i kh\'e1c... D\u7921 a v\'e0o c\'e1i g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 quy t\u7855 c ki\u7875 u g\'ec v\u7853 y? M\'ecnh c\'f3 bi\u7871 t thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i \u273 en kia c\'f3 \'fd ngh\u297 a \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e2u...\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t l\'fac n\'e0y bi\u7879 n b\u7841 ch ho\'e0n to\'e0n v\'f4 \'edch, tr\'e1i l\u7841 i, \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  g\'f3c \u273 \u7897  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, l\u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i m\u7899 i l\'e0 c\'f3 l\'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7845 y \u273 \'e1 ch\u7885 i \u273 \'e1 s\u7869  ch\u7881  khi\u7871 n k\u7871 t qu\u7843  c\'e0ng h\u7887 ng th\'eam, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng ch\u7889 ng l\u7841 i m\u7897 t \u7893  qu\'e1i v\u7853 t kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7853 u \u273 ang \u7903  tr\'ean \u273 \u7883 a b\'e0n c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, an nguy c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u \u273 \u7873 u n\u7855 m trong tay Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, nghe theo \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, l\u7841 i thu\u7853 n theo logic l\'e0m vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\u7869  ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean, ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\u7897  ra \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng cong c\u7847 n c\u7893  kh\'f4ng ch\'fat \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng: "Xin ng\'e0i h\'e3y h\'fat m\'e1u t\'f4i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, ng\'e0i c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n l\u432 u t\'ecnh nh\u432  l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c... Th\u7881 nh c\u7847 u trao \u273 \u7893 i duy nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a t\'f4i l\'e0, s\u7869  \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i mang b\u7841 n c\u7911 a t\'f4i c\'f9ng \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong c\uc0\u259 n ph\'f2ng m\u7901  t\u7889 i, c\u7893  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u l\u7897  ra \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t tr\u7855 ng, thon d\'e0i m\'e0 m\u7873 m m\u7841 i, hu\u7889 ng chi trong l\'f2ng ch\u7911  nh\'e2n \'e1nh m\u7855 t duy nh\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t m\'e0n n\'e0y c\'f2n h\'e0m ch\u7913 a \u7849 n t\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng r\uc0\u7845 t t\u7889 i, hai m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean che kh\u259 n l\u7909 a, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\u7845 t k\u7923  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e9t g\'ec. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\u432 u luy\u7871 n kh\'f4ng r\u7901 i tr\'ean c\u7893  m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t ng\u7901  kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'ecnh b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7885 t t\u7899 i \'f4m l\u7845 y, tim c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c treo l\'ean, trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t ti\u7871 p theo c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'ecnh b\u7883  n\'e9m l\'ean v\u7853 t g\'ec \u273 \'f3 m\u7873 m m\u7873 m \u273 \'e0n h\u7891 i. C\u7853 u s\u7901  th\u7917 , d\u432 \u7899 i tay ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\u417  l\u7909 a, ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t nhanh c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'f3ng m\u7901  bao ph\u7911  ph\'eda tr\'ean, th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u361 ng c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7913 c n\u7863 ng c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng r\'f5 l\u7855 m m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch l\'e0m v\u7853 y c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, nh\u432 ng sau khi nh\u7899  t\u7899 i l\u7901 i h\u7913 a c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n trao \u273 \u7893 i l\u7841 i thu\u7853 n theo n\'e2ng c\u7893  l\'ean l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, s\'e2u trong l\'f2ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c nh\u432  tr\'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'e1nh n\u7863 ng\'97\'97 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n trao \u273 \u7893 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915 ng c\'e1i h\'f4n r\u417 i tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u, m\u7897 t gi\'e2y sau l\'e0n da m\u7887 ng manh b\u7883  r\u259 ng nh\u7885 n \u273 \'e2m th\u7911 ng l\u7847 n n\u7919 a \'97\'97so v\u7899 i l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u7845 p thi\u7871 t h\u417 n r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, r\'f5 r\'e0ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i \u273 \'e3 h\'fat m\'e1u, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh t\u297 nh nh\u432  l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 m\'ea ho\u7863 c, kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u7913 c ch\u7871  kh\'e1t v\u7885 ng trong l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c v\'f4 th\u7913 c d\'f9ng hai tay si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t b\u7843  vai \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, trong l\'fac ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e0n tay \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\u432  trong gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng du t\u7849 u t\u7915 ng ch\'fat vu\u7889 t ve m\'ecnh... Tay tr\'e1i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 eo m\u7897 t v\u7853 t gi\u7889 ng kim lo\u7841 i, h\u7859 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n...\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y d\'f9ng g\u7845 p ba th\u7901 i gian l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bu\'f4ng ra. N\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t c\u7853 u th\u7845 m \u432 \u7899 t kh\u259 n l\u7909 a \u273 en che m\u7855 t, c\'f3 m\u7897 t \'edt c\'f2n men theo g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t l\u259 n xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\'f9ng ng\'f3n tay nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng s\u7901  m\u7843 nh v\u7843 i \u273 en th\u7845 m \u432 \u7899 t, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nhu h\'f2a h\'f4n l\'ean gi\u7885 t n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t tr\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, n\u7881  non th\'ec th\u7847 m t\u7921 a nh\u432  xoa d\u7883 u: "... \u272 \u7915 ng s\u7907 , ta s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n g\'ec th\u432 \u417 ng t\u7893 n ng\u432 \u417 i... N\u417 i \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u432 \u417 ng t\u7893 n ng\u432 \u417 i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m c\uc0\u7911 a h\u7855 n qu\'e1 m\u7913 c tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p tri\u7873 n mi\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'fd th\u7913 c m\u7901  m\u7883 t ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u7847 u "\u272 \u7915 ng s\u7907 " , kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\'f5 nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i ph\'eda sau. L\u7847 n n\'e0y h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 d\'f9ng gi\u7885 ng th\u7853 t m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i lo\u7841 i truy\u7873 n \'e2m m\u7901  \u7843 o, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7903 i v\'ec tinh th\u7847 n m\u7879 t m\u7887 i m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t gi\'e1c ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec s\u7907  h\'e3i, ch\u7881  l\'e0... qu\'e1 k\'edch th\'edch, lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'e0y. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'ec gi\'e1c quan c\u7911 a m\'ecnh m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i x\u7845 u h\u7893 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i ra c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 p t\u7909 c \'f4m s\'e1t vu\u244 \u769 t ve h\u7891 i l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\u7899 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n bu\'f4ng c\u7853 u ra, \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y l\'f9i l\u7841 i \u273 \u7913 ng qua m\u7897 t b\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\'e3y gi\uc0\u7909 a t\u7915  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p s\u7917 a sang m\'e1i t\'f3c t\'e1n lo\u7841 n v\u7899 i \'e1o s\u417 mi b\u7883  gi\u7853 t ra \u273 \'e3 h\u7887 i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m nh\u7845 t: "Ng\'e0i l\'e0 \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? T\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  mang b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a t\'f4i c\'f9ng \u273 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7847 y l\'f2ng ch\u7901  mong l\u7841 i th\u7845 p th\u7887 m b\u7845 t an ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \'e1p \'e1n kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh, ch\u7907 t nghe th\u7845 y thanh \'e2m l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng xa x\'f4i mi\u803 t m\u7901  nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: "Th\u7853 t ng\'e2y th\u417 , bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i h\'f4m nay, \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y, ta \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u417 i v\u7889 n c\'f3 th\u7875  mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec th\'ec l\'e0m, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 do ng\u432 \u417 i d\u7909  d\u7895  ta. Ta v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng th\u7881 nh c\u7847 u c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i, nh\u432 ng ta c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n kh\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng gi\u7853 n, sao c\'f3 th\u7875 ... nh\u432  v\u7853 y. R\'f5 r\'e0ng v\u7915 a th\u7887 a th\'edch h\'fat m\'e1u m\'ecnh xong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7847 m l\u7845 y \'e1o s\u417  mi c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, b\u7903 i v\'ec qu\'e1 d\'f9ng s\u7913 c m\'e0 v\'f2 v\u7843 i trong tay th\'e0nh m\u7897 t c\u7909 c. L\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n n\'fat \'e1o s\u417  mi c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  gi\u7853 t v\u259 ng h\u7871 t, ch\u7881  c\'f2n hai n\'fat tr\'ean c\'f9ng, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng t\'fam hai v\u7841 t \'e1o l\u7841 i, l\u7845 y tay k\'e9o l\u7841 i che \u273 \u7853 y th\'e2n th\u7875 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t l\'fac n\'e0y m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng c\'f3 quy\u7873 n ph\u7843 n kh\'e1ng hay ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7889 i. \u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i kh\'f4ng sai, l\'e0 m\'ecnh qu\'e1 ng\'e2y th\u417 , cho r\u7857 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u b\'ecnh ph\u7909 c h\'f4 h\u7845 p, gi\u7919  v\u7919 ng tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh n\'f3i: "Xin m\u7901 i ng\'e0i n\'f3i, l\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Trong m\uc0\u7897 t th\'e1ng, h\u7841 n \u273 \u7883 nh ba m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ta mu\u7889 n m\'e1u c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i, ng\u432 \u417 i s\u7869  ph\u7843 i t\u7899 i g\u7863 p ta, ta s\u7869  cho ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i \u273 \'f3n ng\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng t\'f4i c\'f2n ph\u7843 i \u273 i h\u7885 c, c\'f2n ph\u7843 i tham gia c\'e1c ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\u7913 c t\'ecm l\'fd do t\u7915  ch\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, nh\u432 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \'e3 cho th\u7845 y th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e0m ph\'e1n, \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng \u273 \'e0m ph\'e1n, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7881  tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u qu\'e2n l\'ednh tan r\'e3, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i b\u7845 t k\'ec \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n g\'ec \'97\'97 trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u \u273 ang ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7911  d\'e0y v\'f2, c\u7853 u th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\u226 \u768 n b\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 m m\'ecnh v\'e0 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n an to\'e0n. M\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng ki\u7875 u c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n t\u7915  ch\u7889 i hay c\'f2 k\'e8 m\u7863 c c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "... \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, t\'f4i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng ng\'e0i, nh\u432 ng ng\'e0i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd \u273 \u7843 m b\u7843 o t\'f4i v\'e0 b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh an r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3 th\uc0\u7875 ." Thanh \'e2m l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m c\u7911 a nam nh\'e2n truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n t\u7915  trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t b\u7897  y ph\u7909 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kho\'e1c l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i. Gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c vang l\'ean: "Ta s\u7869  cho Grey \u273 \u432 a c\'e1c ng\u432 \u417 i r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i ra kh\u7887 i c\u259 n ph\'f2ng kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 ang ch\u7901  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a, gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i b\'ecnh th\u7843 n kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m: "Ng\'e0i c\'f3 th\u7875  th\'e1o kh\u259 n xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 a tay th\'e1o kh\u259 n xu\u7889 ng, \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n s\'e1ng ch\'f3i b\'ean ngo\'e0i khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\'edch \u7913 ng, c\u7853 u l\u7841 i nh\u7855 m ch\u7863 t hai m\u7855 t, qua h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i m\u7903  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u nh\'ecn y ph\u7909 c tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh, \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o kho\'e1c ngo\'e0i nam gi\u7899 i m\'e0u \u273 en ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n nh\u432 ng ch\u234 \u769  t\'e1c c\u7921 c k\u7923  c\u7847 u k\u7923 . B\u7897  y ph\u7909 c n\'e0y v\u7889 n ch\u7881  cho\'e0ng qua tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u, sau khi c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n nhanh ch\'f3ng quay l\u432 ng bu\'f4ng hai v\u7841 t \'e1o m\'ecnh \u273 ang gi\u7919 , m\u7863 c chi\u7871 c \'e1o kho\'e1c ngo\'e0i l\'ean, l\u7841 i nghi\'eam ch\u7881 nh \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i ba n\'fat \'e1o tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c. Y ph\u7909 c n\'e0y c\u7853 u m\u7863 c kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 v\u7915 a ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng so v\u7899 i chi\u7871 c \'e1o s\u417  mi \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  x\'e9 h\u7871 t n\'fat \'e1o kia th\'ec t\u7889 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey nh\'ecn y ph\uc0\u7909 c tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u, \'e1nh m\u7855 t h\u417 i l\'f3e: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, ti\'ean sinh, ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i t\'ecm v\u7883  b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u kia c\u7911 a ng\'e0i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Grey d\uc0\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, mang theo c\u7853 u \u273 i th\u7859 ng v\'e0o s\u7843 nh y\u7871 n h\u7897 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y b\uc0\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed h\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f2n cu\u7891 ng nhi\u7879 t h\u417 n so v\u7899 i l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng tr\'ean l\u7847 u hai nh\'ecn th\u7845 y. Nh\u432 ng k\u7923  d\u7883  ch\'ednh l\'e0 n\u417 i c\u7853 u \u273 i qua, nh\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u ng\u7915 ng \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c \u259 n u\u7889 ng, th\u7859 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean chuy\u7875 n qua m\u7897 t b\'ean, v\'ec b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\'e0 nh\u432 \u7901 ng ra m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\'e0i sau khi th\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  th\'ec kinh ng\u7841 c m\u7903  to m\u7855 t, nh\u432 ng ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n l\'e0 h\u7841  m\u7855 t tr\'e1nh \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat ng\uc0\u7841 c nhi\'ean, l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n qu\'e1 s\u7907  Grey, b\u7903 i v\'ec Grey \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u lu\'f4n bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i c\u7921 c k\u7923  kh\'e1ch quan l\'fd tr\'ed, m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng qu\'e1i v\u7853 t s\u101 \u771  b\u7883  m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i h\u7845 p d\u7851 n. c\u7853 u nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7887 i th\u259 m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: "B\u7885 n h\u7885  h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t s\u7907  \'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i s\u7907  t\'f4i." Grey b\'ecnh th\u7843 n nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y t\u7841 i sao b\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\u7843 i nh\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec b\u7843 n th\'e2n ng\'e0i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t," Ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng t\'f3c x\'e1m quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i y\'ean l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, "B\'e2y gi\u7901  to\'e0n th\'e2n ng\'e0i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\'f9i h\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia d\'f9 cho kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 m\'f9i h\u432 \u417 ng thu\u7897 c v\u7873  Emmer Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng th\'ec c\u361 ng s\u7869  kinh s\u7907  kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i thu\u7897 c v\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883  cao kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 To\'e0n th\'e2n \uc0\u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\'f9i h\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 ? Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe v\u7853 y c\'f3 ch\'fat m\u7901  m\u7883 t k\'e9o k\'e9o qu\u7847 n \'e1o tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o n\'e0y sao? B\u7903 i v\'ec b\u7897  y ph\u7909 c n\'e0y thu\u7897 c v\u7873  v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng trong mi\u7879 ng nh\u7919 ng k\u7867  kia? Ch\u7911  nh\'e2n b\'e0n tay kia, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i h\'fat m\'e1u m\'ecnh l\u7841 i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng th\u7843  b\u7885 n h\u7885  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c?\cb1 \
