\cb3 Grey gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7895  Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, kh\'f4ng ch\u7847 n ch\u7915  t\'ecm ki\u7871 m xung quanh m\'e0 \u273 i th\u7859 ng v\u7873  h\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7897 t g\'f3c nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 G\'f3c kia r\uc0\u7845 t \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7871 c m\u7855 t li\u7873 n th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Giang \u272 i\u7873 n. S\u7855 c m\u7863 t h\u7855 n h\u417 i t\'e1i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 do b\u7883  d\u7885 a hay l\'e0 do m\u7845 t m\'e1u qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u, hai l\u7895  th\u7911 ng r\u432 \u7899 m m\'e1u r\u7845 t nh\u7887  tr\'ean c\u7893  h\u432 \u7899 ng ra ngo\'e0i c\'e0ng th\'eam thu h\'fat s\u7921  ch\'fa \'fd. \'dd th\u7913 c h\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7881 nh t\'e1o l\u7855 m, ng\u7891 i tr\'ean m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c gh\u7871  d\u7921 a v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng, m\u7897 t v\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u7867  \u273 \u7865 p c\'f3 m\'e1i t\'f3c d\'e0i m\'e0u v\'e0ng n\'e2u \u273 ang n\u7917 a ng\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t h\u7855 n, li\u7871 m l\'e1p v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ean c\u7893  h\u7855 n, \'e1nh m\u7855 t m\'e0u l\u7909 c kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng \u273 \u7843 o quanh ph\'eda tr\'ean, t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\u361 ng \u273 ang t\'ecm ki\u7871 m n\u417 i h\u7841  mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey mang theo Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i t\u7899 i. D\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\u7883  phu nh\'e2n xinh \u273 \u7865 p tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t n\'e0y, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "Xin l\u7895 i, Linda, t\'f4i mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh n\'e0y \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c bu\'f4ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, ng\u7891 i th\u7859 ng l\'ean, g\u7849 y g\u7849 y t\'f3c d\'e0i r\u7911  tr\'ean vai: "Grey? \'d4ng mu\u7889 n c\u432 \u7899 p ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i t\'f4i sao? T\'f4i v\u7915 a m\u7899 i l\u7845 y t\u7915  ch\u7895  m\u7845 y Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c nh\u7887  tu\u7893 i kia t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, v\u7851 n c\'f2n ch\u432 a h\u432 \u7903 ng qua m\'f9i v\u7883 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 \uc0\u7843  nh\'fan vai: "\'cdt nh\u7845 t ph\u7843 i ch\'fa \'fd th\u7913  t\u7921  tr\u432 \u7899 c sau ch\u7913 , t\u7863 ng cho \'f4ng m\u7897 t l\'e1t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875 ." \u7842  v\'e0 Grey \u273 \u7859 ng c\u7845 p t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhau, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i nh\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y r\u7891 i v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  ng\u259 n c\u7843 n, lo l\u7855 ng nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Grey.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 l\'fac n\'e0y Linda c\uc0\u361 ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u l\u7909 c h\u7913 ng th\'fa nh\'ecn c\u7853 u ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m, thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i Grey: "Ho\u7863 c l\'e0 l\u7845 y c\u7853 u b\'e9 \'f4ng mang \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f4\u777 i c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey ch\uc0\u7881  y\'ean l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn \u7843 : "C\'f4 \u273 i\'ean r\u7891 i sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Linda \uc0\u273 ang say m\'ea trong m\'f9i m\'e1u l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, \u7843  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c thay \u273 \u7893 i s\u7855 c m\u7863 t, ch\u7881  v\'e0o Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng t\'f3c x\'e1m do d\u7921  d\'f2 h\u7887 i: "C\u7853 u ta... ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey nh\uc0\u432  nh\'ecn ra nghi ng\u7901  c\u7911 a \u7843 , m\u7863 t v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ch\'fat g\u7907 n s\'f3ng: "Kh\'f4ng sai. L\'e0 \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  k\'eau t\'f4i \u273 \u432 a hai nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i n\'e0y r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i. B\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u7901 i cho t\'f4i ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Linda l\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y nhanh ch\'f3ng nh\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 \u7875  cho Giang \u272 i\u7873 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 i l\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c, tay tr\'e1i d\'ednh ch\'fat n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh b\'f4i l\'ean v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7903 i y ph\u7909 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh qu\u7845 n h\u7855 n l\u7841 i, l\u7841 i qu\u7923  m\u7897 t g\u7889 i ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, d\'f9ng tay ph\u7843 i n\'e2ng c\u7857 m Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng v\'e0o \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en m\u7901  m\u7883 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n ch\u7853 m r\'e3i n\'f3i: "H\'f4m nay kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec ph\'e1t sinh, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  tham gia m\u7897 t ti\u7879 c r\u432 \u7907 u nh\'e0m ch\'e1n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng u\u7889 ng qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean, nh\u7899  ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n m\'ea mang g\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, sau \u273 \'f3 \'f4m \u273 \u7847 u, nh\u7855 m hai m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, c\'f3 ch\'fat \u273 au r\'ean r\u7881  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, t\u7921 a l\u432 ng v\'e0o gh\u7871  ng\u7891 i b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean lo l\uc0\u7855 ng \u273 i ra ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c xem x\'e9t t\'ecnh h\'ecnh c\u7911 a b\u7841 n m\'ecnh, l\'fac n\'e0y mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ean c\u7893  Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i m\u7897 t v\u7879 t \u273 \u7887  nh\u7841 t. M\u7863 t h\u7855 n \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng, t\u7921 a l\u432 ng v\'e0o gh\u7871  ng\u7891 i nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 ng\u7911  say, m\u7897 t b\u7897  d\'e1ng say kh\u432 \u7899 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 i h\'f4m nay h\u7855 n qu\u7843  th\u7921 c ng\u7845 m r\u432 \u7907 u, m\'e0 b\'e2y gi\u7901  ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c h\u7855 n khi\u7871 n h\u7855 n tin t\u432 \u7903 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 say, c\u361 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u7913 ng l\'e0m ra ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng khi th\u7853 t s\u7921  say, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  th\'f4i mi\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7917  n\'e2ng b\u7841 n m\'ecnh d\u7853 y, nh\u432 ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n cao h\u417 n c\u7853 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng x\u432 \u417 ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n ng\'e3 v\'e0o gh\u7871 , to\'e0n th\'e2n v\'f4 l\u7921 c, c\u7853 u th\u7917  hai l\u7847 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\'e0nh c\'f4ng. Grey \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean th\u7845 y th\u7871  li\u7873 n kh\u7869  g\u7853 p l\u432 ng l\u7841 i, d\u7877  d\'e0ng khi\'eang Giang \u272 i\u7873 n l\'ean, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i d\'f9ng tay kia ra hi\u7879 u \'fd b\u7843 o Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo sau. S\u7913 c m\u7841 nh c\u7911 a huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c x\'e1c th\u7921 c kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 th\u7913  nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  so s\'e1nh.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "Sao v\uc0\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\u7841 i l\'e0nh nhanh nh\u432  v\u7853 y? Kh\'f4ng sao n\u7919 a \u432 ?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 u\u7893 i theo h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "D\uc0\u7883 ch th\u7875  c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p cao c\u361 ng c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng l\'e0m l\'e0nh v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng." Grey gi\u7843 i th\'edch \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i d\'f9ng \'e1nh m\u7855 t m\'e0u lam li\u7871 c c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i, "T\'f4i ngh\u297  ng\'e0i bi\u7871 t r\u7845 t r\'f5 ch\u7913 , d\'f9 sao d\u7883 ch th\u7875  c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  h\u7859 n l\'e0 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  h\u417 n t\'f4i m\u7899 i ph\u7843 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7919 ng s\u7901 , nh\u7899  t\u7899 i hai l\u7847 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia h\'fat m\'e1u m\'ecnh xong \u273 \u7873 u c\u7849 n th\u7853 n li\u7871 m xung quanh d\u7845 u r\u259 ng. Th\'ec ra l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7871 , h\u7855 n \u273 ang gi\'fap m\'ecnh l\'e0m l\'e0nh v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7853 t xin l\u7895 i, t\'f4i c\'f2n mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\'f4 g\'e1i m\u7863 c v\'e1y tr\u7855 ng c\u361 ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y c\'f9ng ch\'fang t\'f4i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f4 \u7845 y sao r\u7891 i?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n h\u7887 i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh c\u7911 a Emily.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f4 ta h\uc0\u7859 n l\'e0 t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n tham gia." Grey kh\'f4ng ch\'fat c\u7843 m x\'fac tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, "H\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f3 l\u7869  ng\'e0i c\u361 ng nh\u7899 , \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  ch\u7881  \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd cho ng\'e0i mang th\'eam m\u7897 t con m\u7891 i r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, c\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh gi\u7919 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng \'97\'97 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\u7883  kia \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  t\u7847 n su\u7845 t \u259 n u\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, c\'f3 hay th\'e8m \u259 n kh\'f4ng, n\u7871 u h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n \u259 n ba b\u7919 a ng\'e0y th\'eam m\u7897 t b\u7919 a khuya, m\u7895 i b\u7919 a \u273 \u7873 u mu\u7889 n h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u th\'ec l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o? C\u7853 u mu\u7889 n n\'f3i b\'f3ng gi\'f3 v\u7899 i Grey nghe ng\'f3ng ch\'fat \u273 \u7881 nh, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u361 ng kh\'ed m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, d\'f9 c\'f3 th\u7871  n\'e0o th\'ec thuy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7847 u c\u7847 u t\u7921  nhi\'ean s\u7869  th\u7859 ng, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i l\'fac n\'e0o mu\u7889 n m\'e1u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u th\'ec s\u7869  ph\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey d\uc0\u7851 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'f4 t\'f4 m\'e0u \u273 en ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 thu h\'fat, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7899  ra \u273 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 chi\u7871 c xe m\'ecnh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a ti\u7879 m hamburger ng\'e0y \u7845 y. Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 Grey \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7879 m hamburger l\'e0m g\'ec, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\u7913  \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, b\'e1n hamburger cho nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i, b\'e1n m\'e1u cho Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c? T\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng n\'e0y l\'e0m Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7903 n h\u7871 t gai \u7889 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi xe ch\uc0\u7841 y ra kh\u7887 i ph\u7841 m vi trang vi\'ean, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i li\u7873 n c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tin nh\uc0\u7855 n li\'ean ti\u7871 p b\'e1o t\u7899 i, c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\'e0i l\'e0 c\u7911 a b\u7841 n h\u7885 c h\u7843 o h\u7919 u v\u7899 i m\u7845 y nh\'f3m chat, c\'f2n c\'f3 tin nh\u7855 n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac m\uc0\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  ba ph\'fat h\u7855 n g\u7917 i li\'ean t\u7909 c ba b\u7889 n tin nh\u7855 n, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 h\u7887 i c\'e1c lo\u7841 i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  "V\u7873  ch\u432 a?" "Ti\u7879 c th\u7871  n\'e0o? Vui kh\'f4ng?", c\'f3 l\u7869  th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, ba b\u7889 n ph\'fat sau kh\'f4ng g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n n\u7919 a, tin nh\u7855 n cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\'e0 l\'fac m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  b\u7843 y ph\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tay c\uc0\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i d\u7915 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t h\u7891 i r\u7891 i v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. \u272 \'e3 tr\u7843 i qua chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e2m t\'ecnh tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 \u432 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u k\'fd t\'fac, d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  tr\u7907  gi\'fap c\u7911 a Grey, Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7895  l\u7921 c d\u7921 ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n l\'ean, \u273 \u7905  h\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng, l\u7845 y th\u7867  ph\'f2ng trong t\'fai qu\u7847 n h\u7855 n ra m\u7903  c\u7917 a, l\u7841 i \u273 \u7863 t h\u7855 n l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, thay \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u7903 i gi\'e0y v\u7899 i \'e1o ngo\'e0i r\u7891 i \u273 \u7855 p k\'edn ch\u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u li\u7871 c nh\'ecn khu\'f4n m\u7863 t ng\u7911  say c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n r\u7891 i \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a th\u7853 t k\u7929  r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  mong h\u7855 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  ch\u7881  l\'e0 u\u7889 ng say nh\u432  th\u7871 , ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c s\u7869  kh\'f4ng sao n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh \u7903  l\u7847 u b\u7889 n, c\u7853 u kh\'f3a c\u7917 a c\u7921 c k\u7923  ch\u7863 t, b\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n ph\'e1 c\u7917 a m\'e0 v\'e0o, l\u7841 i \u273 \'f3ng ch\u7863 t c\u7917 a s\u7893 , hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  ch\u7881  c\u7847 n ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n h\'e0ng x\'f3m c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng r\'e9t m\'e0 run.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi l\'e0m xong t\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843 , c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng gi\u7919 a ph\'f2ng, \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7903 i \'e1o kho\'e1c ngo\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en n\'e9m qua m\u7897 t b\'ean, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i c\u7903 i \'e1o s\u417  mi nh\u259 n nh\u259 n nh\'fam nh\'fam tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e9m th\u7859 ng v\'e0o th\'f9ng r\'e1c, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\u7887 i c\u7847 n kh\'e2u n\'fat \'e1o l\u7841 i, b\u7883  k\'e9o r\'e1ch nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7863 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a. Sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7841 p gi\u7847 y v\'f4 l\u7921 c ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, k\'e9o ch\u259 n tr\'f9m k\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i, ki\'ean \u273 \u7883 nh ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  l\'fac \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n v\u7905  v\u7909 n, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y to\'e0n th\'e2n ph\'e1t run, h\'e0n \'fd tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'e2ng l\'ean t\u7915 ng tr\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 chuy\uc0\u7879 n n\'e0y c\'f2n xa m\u7899 i ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t, \'edt nh\u7845 t l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac c\u7853 u ho\'e0n th\'e0nh \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 m\uc0\u7897 t kh\u7855 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7847 m ngh\u297  m\u7863 c k\u7879  t\u7845 t c\u7843  mua v\'e9 m\'e1y bay v\u7873  n\u432 \u7899 c, m\u7863 c k\u7879  ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh h\u7885 c \u273 \'e3 h\u7885 c m\u7897 t n\u7917 a, c\u361 ng m\u7863 c k\u7879  \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i quy \u273 \u7883 nh h\u7841 ng m\u7909 c trao \u273 \u7893 i c\u7911 a tr\u432 \u7901 ng, d\'f9 c\u7853 u c\'f3 b\u7903 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 b\u7883  tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 u\u7893 i h\u7885 c hay x\u7917  ph\u7841 t hay tr\'ec ho\'e3n ho\'e0n t\u7845 t g\'ec g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng sao h\u7871 t, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7889 n nh\u7919 ng qu\'e1i v\u7853 t kia th\u7853 t xa l\'e0 t\u7889 t r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng r\u7845 t nhanh c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7881 nh t\'e1o l\u7841 i, tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t. Hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  bao nhi\'eau nh\'e2n t\u7889  v\u7899 i quy t\u7855 c b\'ean ngo\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u7873 u ng\u259 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o d\u7877  d\'e0ng \u273 \'e0o t\u7849 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c t\'ecm c\u7843 nh s\'e1t, nh\u432 ng c\u7843 nh s\'e1t n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y s\u7869  tin t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7901 i c\u7853 u n\'f3i sao? S\u7869  qu\u7843 n chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y sao? M\'e0... trong \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p c\'f3 khi n\'e0o c\u361 ng c\'f3 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\'e0 tr\u7897 n v\'e0o kh\'f4ng, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 c\u7845 p cao trong \u273 \'f3? C\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u432 a qu\'ean y\u7871 n h\u7897 i n\'e0y ch\'ednh l\'e0 l\u7845 y danh ngh\u297 a c\'f4ng ty Prius thanh danh hi\u7875 n h\'e1ch m\'e0 t\u7893  ch\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng qu\'e1i v\u7853 t n\'e0y kho\'e1c l\u7899 p v\u7887  da kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c g\'ec nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i, c\'f3 th\u7875  quang minh ch\'ednh \u273 \u7841 i tr\'e0 tr\u7897 n trong x\'e3 h\u7897 i lo\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i, th\u7853 m ch\'ed d\u7921 a v\'e0o tu\u7893 i th\u7885  cao h\u417 n, th\u7901 i gian kinh doanh d\'e0i h\u417 n, s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i h\u417 n c\u7897 ng v\u7899 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng t\u7897 c \u273 \'e0n m\'e0 l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng quy t\u7855 c c\u7911 a x\'e3 h\u7897 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i, v\'ec ch\'ednh m\'ecnh m\'e0 m\u432 u gi\'e0nh \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883  c\'f3 l\u7907 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean vang l\'ean, c\u259 \u769 t \u273 \u432 \u769 t c\u7853 u kh\u7887 i c\'e1c lo\u7841 i \'fd ni\u7879 m h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n trong \u273 \u7847 u. C\u7853 u c\u7847 m l\'ean nh\'ecn, l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. V\u7915 a r\u7891 i h\u7855 n l\u7841 i g\u7917 i m\u7845 y tin nh\u7855 n cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7875  x\'e1c v\'e0 tinh th\u7847 n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 m\u7879 t, song Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n ti\u7871 p \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, t\u7915  trong m\u361 i ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng "Alo" khe kh\u7869 , nh\u432  ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t nh\u7887  r\u7847 m r\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i c\'e1ch s\'f3ng \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i truy\u7873 n t\u7899 i: "H\u7843 ? L\'e0m sao th\u7871 ? Ch\u417 i m\u7879 t \'e0? Sao kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tinh th\u7847 n v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\uc0\u7917 a ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, c\u7889  che gi\u7845 u h\u7855 ng gi\u7885 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3. Sao mu\u7897 n th\u7871  n\'e0y r\u7891 i anh g\u7885 i c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\uc0\u7879 c g\'ec," \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \'f4n nhu n\'f3i, "C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7891 i \'e2m t\'f4i, l\'fac m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  t\'f4i ngh\u297  ch\u7855 c c\u7853 u \u273 ang ch\u417 i vui kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd n\'ean kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 n tin n\u7919 a, nh\u432 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, t\'f4i h\u417 i lo l\u7855 ng cho c\u7853 u cho n\'ean g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i x\'e1c nh\u7853 n th\u7917 ."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 c d\'f9 ch\u7881  l\'e0 l\u7901 i n\'f3i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong ng\u7921 c \u7845 m \'e1p, m\u361 i h\u417 i chua x\'f3t. L\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u v\u7915 a \u273 \'e3 tr\u7843 i qua m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam kinh kh\u7911 ng nh\u7845 t, t\'e2m y\u7871 u \u7899 t nh\u432  t\u7901  gi\u7845 y m\u7887 ng. C\u7853 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng "C\u7843 m \u417 n" .\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 ? T\'f4i v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng \u7893 n." Gi\u7885 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi trong \u273 \'eam \u273 en y\'ean t\u297 nh \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t d\u7877  ch\u7883 u m\'e0 \'eam tai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7889 n m\u7879 t kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n n\'f3i m\u7897 t ch\u7919 , tr\u432 \u7899 c khi hi\u7875 u r\'f5 m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i b\u7845 t c\u7913  ai, nh\u432 ng gi\u7901  ph\'fat n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean r\u7845 t mu\u7889 n n\'f3i h\u7871 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u do d\u7921  l\u7845 y, \u273 \u7855 n \u273 o d\'f9ng t\u7915  th\u259 m d\'f2 m\'e0 h\u7887 i: "Anh \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\u7845 t l\'e2u kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 y gi\'e2y sau m\u7899 i \u273 \'e1p: "Sao \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\u7841 i h\u7887 i th\u7871 ? C\u7853 u g\u7863 p \'e0?" Trong thanh \'e2m kh\'f4ng c\'f2n tho\u7843 i m\'e1i nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'f3 ch\'fat ng\u432 ng tr\u7885 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t n\'ean tr\u7843  l\u7901 i th\u7871  n\'e0o, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang. V\'ec sao Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i h\u7887 i th\u7859 ng m\'ecnh "C\u7853 u g\u7863 p \'e0?", trong m\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, th\u7913  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ch\u7881  l\'e0 h\u432  c\u7845 u ra, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i trong th\u7921 c t\u7871  sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7843 i th\'edch h\u7907 p l\'fd ch\u7881  c\'f3 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i m\u7845 y th\u7913  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c n\'e0y, \'edt nh\u7845 t c\u361 ng x\'e1c nh\u7853 n ch\'fang th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\u7845 t lo l\u7855 ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a: "C\'f3 ph\u7843 i y\u7871 n h\u7897 i t\u7889 i nay c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tham gia? C\u7853 u b\u7883  c\u7855 n?" Thanh \'e2m c\u7911 a h\u7855 n r\u7845 t g\u7845 p, c\'f2n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  che gi\u7845 u h\u7871 t lo l\u7855 ng d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'e2ng." H\uc0\u7887 i th\u259 m b\u7913 c b\'e1ch v\u7897 i v\'e3 nh\u432  v\u7853 y ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i th\'f4i th\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7905  b\u7887  t\'e2m l\'fd ph\'f2ng b\u7883 , b\u7897 c l\u7897  th\u7853 t t\'e2m, th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  t\'edn nhi\u7879 m kh\'f4ng ch\'fat nghi ng\u7901  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\u361 ng cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u361 ng kh\'ed n\'f3i ra m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'f9ng tay che m\u7855 t m\'ecnh, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng \u273 \'e1p: "... Y\u7871 n h\u7897 i kia c\u259 n b\u7843 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 do m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u t\u7893  ch\u7913 c, em \u7903  \u273 \'f3, b\u7883  m\u7897 t Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c h\'fat m\'e1u, hai l\u7847 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7919  \u273 i\u7879 u c\u7853 u c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7845 t \u7893 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  b\'ean kia \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng an \u7911 i: "Kh\'f4ng sao, b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, kh\'f4ng sao c\u7843 , t\u7915  t\u7915  n\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\'f3 s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh k\u7923  d\u7883 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\u7915  t\u7915  an \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7841 i, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng suy ngh\u297  logic k\u7875  l\u7841 i ti\u7873 n c\u259 n h\u7853 u qu\u7843  v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u s\u7907  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia sao? B\u7903 i v\'ec h\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u, c\'f2n tham lam h\'fat hai l\u7847 n?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c nghe xong Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7847 n thu\u7853 t m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean l\u7841 i h\u7887 i c\'e2u n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "S\uc0\u7907 ." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhanh ch\'f3ng nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng \u273 \'e1p, kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y c\u7853 u ch\'e1n gh\'e9t h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng?" H\u7855 n nhu h\'f2a, tho\'e1ng mang ch\'fat d\u7909  d\u7895  c\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... Ch\'e1n gh\'e9t."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, qua gi\'e2y l\'e1t m\u7899 i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng n\'f3i: "T\'f4i \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m b\u7843 o c\u7853 u c\'e1ch nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 xa m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng khuy\'ean c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'ean tham gia y\u7871 n h\u7897 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nghe l\u7901 i t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\uc0\u7887 i nh\'edu m\'e0y: "Anh \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i Alex v\u7899 i y\u7871 n h\u7897 i kia c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi y\'ean l\u7863 ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, "Nh\u432 ng theo mi\'eau t\u7843  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p, kinh nghi\u7879 m v\u7899 i tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c n\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t c\'e1ch xa b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  t\u7889 t h\u417 n. Qu\u7843  nhi\'ean l\'e0 th\u7871 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng n\u7863 ng, ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng v\'e0 l\u7901 i n\'f3i c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7873 u l\u7897  ra h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng h\u7873  gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh r\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 ai? Anh l\'e0 ai? T\u7841 i sao anh l\u7841 i bi\u7871 t nhi\u7873 u v\u7873  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u nh\u432  v\u7853 y?" Sau khi nghe c\u7853 u k\u7875  xong, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng h\u7873  bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n ra n\u7917 a \u273 i\u7875 m kinh ng\u7841 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam kinh kh\u7911 ng n\'e0y trong m\u7855 t h\u7855 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i l\'e0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t t\'f4i t\u7915  l\'e2u r\u7891 i m\'e0." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7921 a h\u7891  c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  \u7913 ng ph\'f3 v\u7899 i c\'e2u h\u7887 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, "Ch\u7881  l\'e0 ngh\u7873  nghi\u7879 p c\u7911 a t\'f4i t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \u7863 c th\'f9. Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i hay ch\u432 a, \u7903  ph\u432 \u417 ng T\'e2y \u273 \u7889 i ngh\u7883 ch v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'f3 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, g\u7885 i l\'e0 th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'e8 nh\u7865 , \'e2m s\u7855 c nhu h\'f2a phun ra ba ch\u7919 : "Ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\'f4i."\cb1 \
