\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh l\'e0 th\uc0\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u?" Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean d\u7845 y l\'ean ch\'fat hy v\u7885 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean bi\u7871 t th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\'e0 g\'ec, h\u7847 u nh\u432  trong t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng t\'e1c ph\u7849 m vi\u7871 t v\u7873  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng thi\u7871 u b\'f3ng d\'e1ng th\u7907  s\u259 n l\u7845 y vi\u7879 c s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u m\'e0 s\u7889 ng. \u272 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\u7843 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 th\u7907  s\u259 n v\u7889 n l\u7845 y vi\u7879 c \u273 i s\u259 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\'e0m ngh\u7873  nghi\u7879 p th\'ec sao? B\u7885 n h\u7885  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i c\'f3 c\'e1ch ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y anh c\'f3 th\u7875  di\u7879 t tr\u7915  nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'f2ng \u273 \u7847 y ch\u7901  mong c\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\u7887 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i tho\'e1ng lo l\u7855 ng, d\'f9 sao h\'f4m nay c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y trong cu\u7897 c c\'f3 ch\u7915 ng h\u417 n tr\u259 m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, m\'e0 c\'f2n kh\'f4ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 s\u7889  l\u432 \u7907 ng t\u7845 t c\u7843  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u7903  Sophus. M\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  \u273 \u417 n th\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7897 c m\'e3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n c\'f2n c\'f3 ... s\u7921  tr\u7907  gi\'fap n\'e0o kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7889 i ph\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nhi\u7873 u qu\'e1i v\u7853 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y hay kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 "Xin l\uc0\u7895 i," c\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7847 m gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i, "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ra tay."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'e2m Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c tr\u7847 m xu\u7889 ng, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'ean gi\u7885 ng: "T\u7841 i sao? Th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u hay sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec sau Th\u7871  chi\u7871 n 2 x\'e3 h\u7897 i lo\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7847 n \u273 i v\'e0o th\u7901 i \u273 \u7841 i \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh, tr\u7853 t t\u7921  \u7903  c\'e1c ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t th\'e0nh l\u7853 p, gi\u7919 a th\u7907  s\u259 n v\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u361 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u7913 ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7841 t th\'e0nh hi\u7879 p \u273 \u7883 nh quang vinh." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m gi\u7843 i th\'edch, " Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'f3 quy \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  r\'e0ng bu\u7897 c h\'e0nh vi c\u7911 a t\u7897 c nh\'e2n, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\'e1i v\u7899 i t\u7897 c quy s\u7869  b\u7883  tr\u7915 ng ph\u7841 t, tr\u7915 ng ph\u7841 t nghi\'eam tr\u7885 ng nh\u7845 t bao g\u7891 m t\u7917  h\'ecnh v\'e0 tr\u7909 c xu\u7845 t kh\u7887 i t\u7897 c. Nh\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c b\u7883  tr\u7909 c xu\u7845 t lang thang n\u7871 u nh\u432  l\'e0m ra h\'e0nh vi nguy h\u7841 i t\u7899 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i c\u361 ng s\u7869  b\u7883  th\u7907  s\u259 n ti\'eau di\u7879 t. T\u7915  \'fd ngh\u297 a n\'e0o \u273 \'f3, th\u7907  s\u259 n \u273 \'f3ng vai tr\'f2 gi\'e1m s\'e1t \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean, sau khi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\'e0m h\u7841 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  b\'e1o cho qu\u7843 n s\u7921  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c cao c\u7845 p \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u417 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c t\u7921  x\u7917  l\'fd n\u7897 i b\u7897 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Hu\uc0\u7889 ng h\u7891  t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i, t\'f4i l\'e0m vi\u7879 c \u7903  Ch\'e2u \'c2u, t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y ch\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  l\'e0 ngh\u7881  ph\'e9p, chuy\u7879 n n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng thu\u7897 c ph\u7841 m vi qu\u7843 n l\'fd c\u7911 a t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  nh\u432  v\u7853 y..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7849 m b\u7849 m, "H\'f4m nay trong y\u7871 n h\u7897 i kia c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u, nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 l\'e0m h\u7841 i sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i xin l\uc0\u7895 i l\'e0m c\u7853 u th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng," Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i, "Nh\u432 ng theo t\'f4i bi\u7871 t, trong s\u7889  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i tham gia y\u7871 n h\u7897 i kia c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0 t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao l\uc0\u7841 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u ch\u7913 ..." \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u nh\u7845 t, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c Alex v\u7899 i Grey c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i Emily l\'e0 t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n tham gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao l\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7843 n nhi\'ean h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i, "\u272 \u7889 i v\u7899 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i m\'e0 n\'f3i, b\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c h\'fat m\'e1u s\u7869  sinh ra kho\'e1i c\u7843 m, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p b\u7853 c c\'e0ng cao s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh c\'e0ng l\u7899 n k\u7929  thu\u7853 t c\'e0ng t\u7889 t c\'e0ng c\'f3 th\u7875  mang \u273 \u7871 n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'e3nh li\u7879 t h\u417 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i sau khi b\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng h\'fat m\'e1u li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 c b\u7845 t c\u7913  gi\'e1 n\'e0o ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 i c\u7847 u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p cao h\'fat m\'e1u m\'ecnh, ch\u7881  v\'ec th\u7875  nghi\u7879 m lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\'ean th\uc0\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y ch\u7881  c\u7847 n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n vui s\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7909  d\u7895  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta tr\u7847 m m\'ea trong \u273 \'f3, tr\u259 m h\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t l\u7907 i t\u7879  nh\u7845 t l\'e0 ma t\'fay, \u273 \'e1nh b\u7841 c. H\u7857 ng ng\'e0y c\u361 ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  tr\u7847 m m\'ea trong phim \u7843 nh, ti\u7875 u thuy\u7871 t, game... Con ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7903  d\u297  th\'edch nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y, ch\u7859 ng qua \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 v\'ec ch\'fang c\'f3 th\u7875  mang \u273 \u7871 n vui v\u7867  cho m\'ecnh. Cho n\'ean d\'f9 bi\u7871 t r\'f5 qu\'e1 tr\u7847 m m\'ea c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  c\'f3 h\u7853 u qu\u7843  kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 nghi\u7879 n. Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7915 ng th\u7875  nghi\u7879 m c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'f4ng d\u7913 t b\u7887  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\'ec v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c. Nh\u432 ng tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tr\u7847 m m\'ea trong chuy\u7879 n b\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c h\'fat m\'e1u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 s\u7903  th\'edch c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'e1nh \u273 \u7891 ng v\u7899 i m\'ea TV hay game.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "Hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  c\'f3 v\'e0i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  cung c\u7845 p t\'e0i ph\'fa, \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883 , quy\u7873 n th\u7871  cho nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i c\'f3 ch\u7845 t m\'e1u \u432 u t\'fa m\'e0 b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\u7915 a \'fd. N\'ean d\'f9 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng sa v\'e0o kho\'e1i c\u7843 m b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u, c\u361 ng r\u7845 t kh\'f3 kh\'f4ng b\u7883  ti\u7873 n quy\u7873 n danh v\u7885 ng l\'e0m \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e2m, do \u273 \'f3 t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n tr\u7903  th\'e0nh n\'f4 l\u7879  cung c\u7845 p m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe xong ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 nh t\u7915 ng tr\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 , nh\u432 ng con ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7903 i v\'ec sa v\'e0o c\'e1c lo\u7841 i d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng, b\u7903 i v\'ec m\'ea mu\u7897 i kho\'e1i c\u7843 m b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u m\'e0 t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n tr\u7903  th\'e0nh huy\u7871 t n\'f4 b\u7883  qu\'e1i v\u7853 t chi ph\u7889 i, b\u7903 i v\'ec d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng m\'ea mu\u7897 i kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o t\u7921  ch\u7911  nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng l\'e0m c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c gi\u7843 i th\'edch: "... M\u7845 y n\u259 m nay c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\'e0i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c ngh\u297  ra kh\'f4ng \'edt c\'e1ch th\u7913 c m\u7899 i, th\u7853 m ch\'ed chuy\u7875 n bi\u7871 n t\u7915  tr\'ean t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng suy ngh\u297  c\u7911 a con ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7847 u t\u432  ch\u7871  t\'e1c m\u7897 t \'edt t\'e1c ph\u7849 m v\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, trong \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\u7879  m\'e0 bi\u7871 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c th\'e0nh s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i tu\u7845 n m\u7929  c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i, th\u7847 n b\'ed l\u7841 i th\'e2m t\'ecnh. V\'ec v\u7853 y m\u7845 y n\u259 m n\'e0y v\u7851 n c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, l\'fac b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u ch\u7859 ng nh\u7919 ng kh\'f4ng s\u7907  h\'e3i, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'f2n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t l\'e3ng m\u7841 n m\'e0 t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n b\u7857 ng l\'f2ng \u7903  b\'ean Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i xong nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y c\'f3 ch\'fat \'e1o n\'e3o nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng l\u7847 m b\u7847 m m\u7897 t c\'e2u "Sao t\'f4i ph\u7843 i v\u7841 ch tr\u7847 n m\u7845 y tr\'f2 h\u7873  n\'e0y v\u7899 i c\u7853 u ch\u7913 ", nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang \u273 \u7855 m ch\'ecm trong t\'e2m t\u432  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng em l\'e0 b\u7883  l\u7915 a," Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i, "Em c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i em nh\u7853 n l\'e0 y\u7871 n h\u7897 i c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  em v\'e0 b\u7841 n em \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u, nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 l\'e0m h\u7841 i sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec c\'f3 \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i sau l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\u7873 n b\u7883  l\u7915 a h\'fat m\'e1u s\u7869  tr\u7847 m m\'ea trong c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y, cho n\'ean t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u, h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\'e0m v\u7853 y c\u361 ng r\u7845 t kh\'f3 b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, cho n\'ean c\'f3 kh\'f4ng \'edt Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t l\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n v\'e0 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911  th\'edch d\'f9ng c\'e1ch n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  t\'ecm ki\u7871 m con m\u7891 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'f3i, "Nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e2y x\'e1c th\u7921 c l\'e0 c\'e1ch l\'e0m kh\'f4ng tu\'e2n theo quy \u273 \u7883 nh, t\'f4i s\u7869  ngh\u297  c\'e1ch t\u7889  c\'e1o nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \'f3 v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p cao, x\u7917  l\'fd b\u7885 n ch\'fang."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 th\'f4ng tin l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ph\u7845 n kh\u7903 i nh\u7845 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'eam nay. C\u7853 u m\u7845 p m\'e1y m\'f4i: "Cho n\'ean em c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng kia \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Chuy\uc0\u7879 n n\'e0y ch\u7855 c kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c," Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng ch\'fat khoan nh\u432 \u7907 ng t\u7915  ch\u7889 i c\u7853 u, "\u431 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh, c\u7853 u v\u7899 i h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7841 t th\'e0nh trao \u273 \u7893 i, \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 a b\u7841 n m\'ecnh \u273 i r\u7891 i, c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh sau \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng anh bi\u7871 t r\'f5 chuy\u7879 n l\u7847 n n\'e0y em c\u259 n b\u7843 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i m\'e0!"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tuy l\'e0 v\uc0\u7853 y," Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  th\u7903  d\'e0i, "A Di\'ean, tr\'ean th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i l\'fd nh\u432  th\u7871 , \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\'f4i \u273 \'e1nh kh\'f4ng l\u7841 i v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia. Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c Emmer \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7885 i l\'e0 sinh v\u7853 t h\u7855 c \'e1m c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u432 \u417 ng th\u7901 i, h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 l\'e0m kh\'f3 d\u7877  c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7853 u t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean khi\'eau kh\'edch ho\u7863 c l\'e0m tr\'e1i h\u7855 n, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\'fap \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 G\uc0\u7863 p Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927 , g\u7863 p th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\u7851 n ng\'e2y th\u417  cho r\u7857 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\'fap m\'ecnh b\u7843 o v\u7879  ch\'ednh ngh\u297 a l\u7845 y l\u7841 i c\'f4ng \u273 \u7841 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\'fd tr\'ed Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng hi\u7875 u r\'f5 m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng th\u7875  qu\'e1 o\'e1n tr\'e1ch Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 th\'e0nh th\u7853 t n\'f3i v\u7899 i m\'ecnh h\u7855 n qu\u7843  th\u7921 c kh\u7843  n\u259 ng c\'f3 h\u7841 n, ch\'ednh m\'ecnh c\u361 ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i minh b\u7841 ch t\'ecnh h\'ecnh hi\u7879 n gi\u7901 , ph\u7843 i th\'f4ng c\u7843 m cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7859 ng ph\u7843 i bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7889 t x\u7845 u sao.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Do d\uc0\u7921  m\u7897 t l\'e1t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng chuy\u7879 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7847 u lo nh\u7845 t: "Nh\u432 ng m\'e0, h\u7855 n n\'f3i ba m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y ti\u7871 p theo khi n\'e0o h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n h\'fat m\'e1u em s\u7869  ph\u7843 i \u273 i g\u7863 p h\u7855 n. Th\u7901 i gian l\'e2u d\'e0i, em s\u7907  em c\u361 ng s\u7869  tr\u7903  n\'ean tr\u7847 m m\'ea chuy\u7879 n b\u7883  h\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u... \u272 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t, em bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i nghi\u7879 n b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o t\u7921  ch\u7911  th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Y\uc0\u7871 t h\u7847 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7895 ng nh\'fac nh\'edch m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u n\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t, l\'fac b\u7883  h\u7855 n c\u7855 n c\u7853 u c\'f3 tho\u7843 i m\'e1i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i n\'f3ng l\'ean, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\'e2n th\u7875  theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng m\'e0 h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng: "... V\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  n\'e0y c\'f3 quan tr\u7885 ng kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "R\uc0\u7845 t quan tr\u7885 ng, c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i n\'f3i chi ti\u7871 t cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t." Thanh \'e2m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe v\'e0o tai v\u7851 n y\'ean \u7843  nh\u432  c\u361 , "Kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 b\u7845 t k\u7923  gi\u7845 u gi\u7871 m n\'e0o, l\'fac b\u7883  h\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u, c\u7853 u c\'f3 tho\u7843 i m\'e1i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7883 u n\u7893 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  che gi\u7845 u m\'e0 che m\u7855 t, t\u7915  trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng ngh\u7865 n r\u7845 t nh\u7887 . C\u7853 u t\u7915  t\u7915  nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, cam ch\u7883 u \u273 \'e1p: "Tho\u7843 i m\'e1i... R\u7845 t tho\u7843 i m\'e1i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3 bao nhi\'eau tho\uc0\u7843 i m\'e1i?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng d\u7909  d\u7895  c\u7853 u n\'f3i ra th\'eam c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u l\u7901 i ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o, "N\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t, khi \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  bay l\'ean tr\u7901 i, nh\u432  l\'e0...c\'f9ng linh h\u7891 n h\u7855 n ch\u7841 m v\'e0o nhau, ho\'e0n to\'e0n h\u7907 p th\'e0nh m\u7897 t th\u7875 ... ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y b\u7883  h\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c khi \u273 \'f3, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ph\u7843 i ph\u417 i b\'e0y nh\u7919 ng c\u7843 m x\'fac x\u7845 u h\u7893  nh\u7845 t trong l\'f2ng c\'f9ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c lo l\u7855 ng s\u7907  h\'e3i cho t\u432 \u417 ng lai b\u7913 c b\'e1ch \u273 \u7871 n c\u7853 u g\u7847 n nh\u432  mu\u7889 n kh\'f3c l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, em s\u7869  nghi\u7879 n sao?" Gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 ch\'fat ngh\'e8n ngh\u7865 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "S\uc0\u7869  kh\'f4ng." \u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1p \'e1n h\'e0i l\'f2ng, k\'ecm l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  khi c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7929  m\'e3n, r\u259 ng nanh b\'e9n nh\u7885 n kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hi\u7879 n ra."Th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u" kh\u7869  li\u7871 m r\u259 ng, kh\'f4ng c\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u432  v\u7883  ti\'eau h\u7891 n th\u7921 c c\u7889 t gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kho\'e1i c\u7843 m khi d\'f9ng r\u259 ng nh\u7885 n \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o trong c\u417  th\u7875  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t mu\u7889 n hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 i \u273 \'f3n ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7903  l\u7841 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "S\uc0\u7869  kh\'f4ng, c\'f2n t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng l\u7863 p l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng ta cam \u273 oan v\u7899 i em, l\u7847 n sau b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh em s\u7869  c\'e0ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i h\u417 n. B\u7903 i v\'ec ta kh\'f4ng n\u7905  l\'e0m em m\'ea man t\'e2m tr\'ed, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mu\u7889 n nh\'ecn em v\'ec ta m\'e0... \'fd lo\u7841 n t\'ecnh m\'ea.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi ch\uc0\u7845 m d\u7913 t tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'ec \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 r\u7841 ng s\'e1ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i c\'f9ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n l\'e2u nh\u432  th\u7871 . Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i an \u7911 i c\u7853 u th\u7853 t l\'e2u, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi nghe ra trong gi\u7885 ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 ch\'fat bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  m\u7899 i ch\'fac c\u7853 u ng\u7911  ngon r\u7891 i c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean lo l\uc0\u7855 ng s\u7921  t\'ecnh, s\'e1ng h\'f4m sau ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n t\'e1m gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, \'f4m ch\u259 n ng\u7891 i h\u7891 i l\'e2u, h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7901 i t\u7889 i qua Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'ecnh th\'e0nh s\u7921  \u273 \u7889 i l\u7853 p r\'f5 n\'e9t v\u7899 i s\u7921  sa s\'fat tinh th\u7847 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ch\'ednh l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, h\'f4m qua ng\u7919  kh\'ed h\u7855 n tuy r\u7857 ng r\u7845 t \'f4n nhu, tuy r\u7857 ng li\'ean t\u7909 c tr\u7845 n an m\'ecnh, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i tho\'e1ng l\u7897  ra v\u7867  ph\u7845 n ch\u7845 n c\'f9ng vui v\u7867  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  che gi\u7845 u, t\u7921 a nh\u432  \u273 \'eam qua h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'f3 r\u7845 t vui. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u h\'f4m qua b\u7843 n th\'e2n qu\'e1 m\u7879 t m\u7887 i, kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t k\u7923  di\u7879 u, b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i x\'f4ng nh\u7847 m v\'e0o y\u7871 n h\u7897 i c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, h\'e0ng x\'f3m th\'ec c\u361 ng l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, b\u7841 n tr\'ean m\u7841 ng c\u417  duy\'ean x\u7843 o h\u7907 p quen bi\u7871 t v\u7853 y m\'e0 c\u361 ng l\'e0 th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927 \'97\'97 m\u7897 t th\u7907  s\u259 n th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e1nh kh\'f4ng l\u7841 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927 . Ai m\'e0 bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y g\u7863 p qu\u7927  r\u7891 i s\u7869  g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i c\'e1i g\'ec kh\'e1c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh tinh th\u7847 n xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o, r\u7917 a m\u7863 t qua loa r\u7891 i nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 i xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u ph\'f2ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p qu\'e9t th\u7867  ph\'f2ng \u273 i v\'e0o \'97\'97h\'f4m qua c\u7853 u v\'ec ph\'f2ng ng\u7915 a v\u7841 n nh\u7845 t n\'ean \u273 \'e3 c\u7847 m th\u7867  ph\'f2ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n v\u7851 n \u273 ang ng\u7911  say tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
