\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n l\u7849 m b\u7849 m tr\'e1nh n\'e9 tay c\u7853 u, hai tay kh\u7869  g\u7841 t \u273 i, qua m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng m\u7899 i ng\'e1i ng\u7911  m\u7901  m\u7883 t ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 ? Sao s\u7899 m th\u7871  m\'e0 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i r\u7891 i? C\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \'e0?"\cb1 \
