\
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i l\'e0 u\u7889 ng nhi\u7873 u qu\'e1 sao? C\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec ch\u7913 ." Giang \u272 i\u7873 n ch\u7859 ng h\u7873  \u273 \u7875  \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'e2m th\uc0\u7847 m d\'e3n ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i, th\u259 m d\'f2 h\u7887 i: "Y\u7871 n h\u7897 i h\'f4m qua c\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  r\'f5 kh\'f4ng? Sau khi t\'e1ch kh\u7887 i t\'f4i c\u7853 u \u273 i \u273 \'e2u? T\'f4i t\'ecm c\u7853 u c\u7843  bu\u7893 i \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 u\u7889 ng ch\'fat r\u432 \u7907 u th\'f4i, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec n\u7919 a, qu\'ean h\u7871 t r\u7891 i." Giang \u272 i\u7873 n v\u7895  tr\'e1n, "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, h\'ecnh nh\u432  t\'f4i nh\u7899  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\u7929  nh\'e2n n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i m\u7855 t xanh l\'e1 t\'f3c d\'e0i m\'e0u v\'e0ng n\'e2u h\'f4n t\'f4i. Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\'e0 c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 a t\'f4i v\u7873  \'e0? \u272 \'e1m Alex \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7929  nh\'e2n n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i kia thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a \u273 \'e3 \u259 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7845 y. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng hi\u7875 u h\u7859 n l\'e0 c\'e1ch Grey s\u7917  d\u7909 ng t\u7889 i qua \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n qu\'ean chuy\u7879 n v\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, v\u7873  y\u7871 n h\u7897 i m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng t\u7889 t, nh\u7919 ng k\'fd \u7913 c \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n vui v\u7867 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 t\'f4i \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u v\u7873 . Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u sau n\'e0y \u273 \u7915 ng ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i \u273 \'e1m Alex kia n\u7919 a, h\'f4m qua t\'f4i nh\'ecn ra b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n l\u7841 i h\u7887 i c\u7853 u v\'ec sao l\u7841 i n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, b\u7883  Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i m\u7845 y c\'e2u l\u7915 a l\u7915 a g\u7841 t g\u7841 t th\'e0nh c\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi x\'e1c nh\uc0\u7853 n Giang \u272 i\u7873 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng sao, Tr\'ec Di\'ean coi nh\u432  tr\'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t g\'e1nh n\u7863 ng, th\u7915 a d\u7883 p Giang \u272 i\u7873 n r\u7917 a m\u7863 t li\u7873 n r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i ph\'f2ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 ang chu\u7849 n b\u7883  qu\'e9t th\u7867  m\u7903  c\u7917 a l\u7841 i \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i Alex t\u7915  s\'e1t v\'e1ch \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a \u273 i ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng c\u417  b\u7855 p to\'e0n th\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m qua m\uc0\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i Alex c\'f3 l\u7869  khuya m\u7899 i v\u7873 , l\'fac c\u7853 u \u273 i ng\u7911  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873 , nh\u432 ng h\'f4m nay th\u7847 n th\'e1i Alex v\u7851 n s\'e1ng l\'e1ng nh\u432  c\u361 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  qu\u7843  nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i d\uc0\u7921  ki\u7871 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, h\u7855 n v\u7853 y m\'e0 ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng ch\'e0o h\u7887 i: "N\'e0y, Jerry, bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng t\u7889 t l\'e0nh. H\'f4m qua c\u7853 u v\u7899 i Kevin v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 c\'f2n nh\u7899  ai \u273 \u432 a c\'e1c c\u7853 u v\u7873  kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7919 ng s\u7901 , l\u7853 p t\u7913 c t\u7881 nh h\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'f3 quy \u273 \u7883 nh na n\'e1 ki\u7875 u "Kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7871 n s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c ", cho n\'ean h\'f4m qua Grey m\u7899 i x\'f3a tr\'ed nh\u7899  c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n. Alex kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng kia c\'f2n c\'f3 \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh h\'fat m\'e1u ba m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y, v\'ec v\u7853 y t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  x\'f3a tr\'ed nh\u7899 ? Cho n\'ean hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  nhi\'ean gi\u7843  v\u7901  nh\u432  ch\u432 a c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec ph\'e1t sinh? Gi\u7843  l\'e0m b\u7841 n h\u7885 c th\'e2n thi\u7871 t l\'e1ng gi\u7873 ng nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh r\u7845 t b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec l\u7841 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "Ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua ch\u417 i vui qu\'e1, kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd ti\u7871 p \u273 \'e3i c\'e1c c\u7853 u. C\'e1c c\u7853 u ch\u417 i c\'f3 vui kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  th\u7853 t h\u7855 n cho r\u7857 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  x\'f3a t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c k\'fd \u7913 c li\'ean quan, b\u7903 i v\'ec h\u7855 n tin ch\u7855 c r\u7857 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer s\u7869  kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p m\u7897 t nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i nh\u7899  r\'f5 s\u7921  hi\u7879 n h\u7919 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i s\u7869  th\'f4ng b\'e1o chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a \u273 \'e1m Alex cho Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p tr\'ean x\u7917  l\'fd, v\'ec v\u7853 y b\u7843 n th\'e2n tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7847 n y\'ean l\u7863 ng theo d\'f5i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh ki\'ean nh\u7851 n ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i. \u272 \u7875  tr\'e1nh ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p, tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t c\u7913  t\u7841 m th\u7901 i gi\u7843  v\u7901  kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  r\'f5 chuy\u7879 n h\'f4m qua, l\u7841 i \'e2m th\u7847 m gi\u7919  kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 , n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ai m\'e0 bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'e0y sau khi b\u7883  k\'e9o da m\u7863 t xu\u7889 ng s\u7869  l\'e0m ra lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n g\'ec kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  l\'e0m v\u7853 y, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i trong l\'f2ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\'ednh to\'e1n nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u qu\u7865 t th\u7867  ph\'f2ng m\u7903  c\u7917 a, tay d\u7921 a l\'ean v\'e1n c\u7917 a, nh\'ecn Alex c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  n\'f3i: "Ch\u7855 c l\'e0 t\'f4i u\u7889 ng nhi\u7873 u qu\'e1, l\'fac t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  r\'f5, h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 m\u7897 t v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh t\'f3c x\'e1m \u273 \u432 a b\u7885 n t\'f4i v\u7873  th\'ec ph\u7843 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u gi\u7843  v\u7901  nh\u432  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7899  ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'f3, n\'f3i v\u7899 i Alex: "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7913  n\'e0y mu\u7889 n cho c\u7853 u xem, c\u7853 u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y ch\u7901  t\'f4i ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i xong \uc0\u273 i v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng, m\u7897 t l\'e1t sau c\u7847 m m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o kho\'e1c ngo\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en \u273 i ra: "Alex, c\u7853 u c\'f3 bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 \'e1o c\u7911 a v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh n\'e0o kh\'f4ng? L\'fac t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i t\'f4i th\u7845 y m\'ecnh \u273 ang m\u7863 c chi\u7871 c \'e1o n\'e0y. Ch\u7845 t \'e1o kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , t\'f4i ngh\u297  n\'ean t\'ecm d\u7883 p tr\u7843  l\u7841 i cho ch\u7911  nh\'e2n c\u7911 a n\'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7875  c\u7853 u c\'e1o m\u432 \u7907 n oai h\'f9m m\u7897 t l\u7847 n \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng kia c\u361 ng ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7889 t l\'e0nh g\'ec, nh\u432 ng \u273 \'eam qua, t\u7915  th\u7847 n th\'e1i c\u7917  ch\u7881  c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c g\u7863 p tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\'f9ng v\u7899 i th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  \u273 \u7897 t bi\u7871 n c\u7911 a Linda sau khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ho\u7863 c ng\u7917 i th\u7845 y kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u7911 a b\u7897  y ph\u7909 c n\'e0y, xem ra v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia r\u7845 t c\'f3 \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883 , \u273 \'e1m Alex c\u361 ng s\u7907  h\u7855 n, cho n\'ean l\'fac \u273 \'f3 Grey m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng mang m\'ecnh t\u7915  trong tay b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\u7897 i b\u7897  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c s\u7869  d\'f9ng bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p g\'ec x\u7917  ph\u7841 t \u273 \'e1m Alex, c\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7889  gi\'e1c c\'f3 \'edch hay kh\'f4ng, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 c\u7913  khi\u7871 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  t\u432 \u7903 ng nh\u7847 m r\u7857 ng v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia c\'f3 ch\'fat quan t\'e2m \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t v\u7899 i m\'ecnh ho\u7863 c \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n m\'ecnh th\'ec m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7841 o t\'e1c d\u7909 ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh b\u7843 o v\u7879  b\u7843 n th\'e2n, \'edt nh\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\'f9y ti\u7879 n l\u7841 i c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7891  v\u7899 i m\'ecnh ho\u7863 c ra tay v\u7899 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Theo nh\uc0\u432  s\u7921  gi\'e1o d\u7909 c t\u7915  nh\u7887  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u m\'e0 n\'f3i, l\'e0m nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang l\u7855 m, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  qu\u7843 n nhi\u7873 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f2n c\'f3, kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i l\'e0 t\'f4i n\'f3i nh\'e9, em g\'e1i Sophus nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh th\u7853 t \u273 \u7845 y." Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7903  m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7847 y n\u7897 i h\'e0m, nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u v\u7873  ph\'eda Alex l\u7897  ra c\u7847 n c\u7893  c\'f3 m\u7897 t d\u7845 u h\'f4n l\u7899 n m\'e0u \u273 \u7887 , "L\'fac s\'e1ng soi g\u432 \u417 ng gi\u7853 t h\u7871 t c\u7843  m\'ecnh, t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 do em g\'e1i n\'e0o l\'e0m \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\uc0\u7897  ra ph\u7847 n c\u7893  v\u7899 i qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u v\u7889 n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n c\u7921 c k\u7923  nguy hi\u7875 m, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng Alex c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901  t\u7841 i \u273 \'f3, m\u7897 t c\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng nh\u7887  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng \u273 \u7897 ng c\u417  m\u7863 t c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c: "... T\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7897  y ph\u7909 c n\'e0y l\'e0 c\u7911 a v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh n\'e0o, hay l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u c\u7913  c\u7845 t \u273 i \u273 \'e3."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch, c\u7853 u m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i, h\'e0i l\'f2ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c t\'e1n g\u7851 u m\u7845 y c\'e2u v\u7899 i qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u nguy hi\u7875 m n\'e0y r\u7891 i c\'e1o bi\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , nhanh ch\'f3ng kh\'f3a ch\u7863 t c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, sau \u273 \'f3 d\u7921 a l\u432 ng v\'e0o c\u7917 a h\'edt s\'e2u hai h\u417 i th\u7853 t l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  b\'ecnh t\u297 nh nh\u432  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7853 u bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n, tuy r\u7857 ng s\u7869  kinh s\u7907 , nh\u432 ng l\'fac \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i Alex, c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7907  h\'e3i theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng\'97\'97 \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t con qu\'e1i v\u7853 t, m\u7897 t con qu\'e1i v\u7853 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tim \u273 \u7853 p, h\'fat m\'e1u ng\u432 \u417 \u768 i, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  b\u7873  ngo\'e0i ra th\'ec ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'e1c con ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\'f9ng m\u7897 t tay che m\u7863 t, \u273 \u7847 u d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\'e1nh c\u7917 a sau l\u432 ng v\'f4 l\u7921 c r\'ean r\u7881  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i trong b\u7909 ng \'e2m th\u7847 m ph\u7881  nh\u7893  b\u7843 n th\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t l\'e0 ti ti\u7879 n, m\'ecnh b\u7883  m\u7897 t t\'ean Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  \u273 \u7871 n ngay c\u7843  m\u7863 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7897  ra h\'f4n th\'e0nh c\'e1i d\u7841 ng n\'e0y, th\u7871  m\'e0 v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i ph\u417 i d\u7845 u v\u7871 t ra cho m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'e1c nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\'ec mu\u7889 n t\u7853 n kh\u7843  n\u259 ng cam \u273 oan b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7869  an to\'e0n h\u417 n ch\'fat \u273 \u7881 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex bi\uc0\u7871 t c\u7853 u b\u7883  mang \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7875  g\u7863 p ai, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \'e1m ch\u7881  h\u7855 n l\'fac cu\u7889 i l\'e0 Grey \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u v\u7873 , cho n\'ean h\u7855 n m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  suy \u273 o\'e1n nh\u7919 ng d\u7845 u v\u7871 t n\u7885  ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 do v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia t\u7841 o th\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'f4m \uc0\u273 \u226 \u768 u g\u244 \u769 i cu\u7897 n l\u7841 i ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\'f4 c\'f9ng \u7911 y khu\u7845 t, tuy r\u7857 ng t\u7915  nh\u7887  cha m\u7865  c\u7853 u d\u7841 y c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i ki\'ean c\u432 \u7901 ng, ph\u7843 i t\u7921  ch\u7883 u tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m v\u7899 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u7911 y khu\u7845 t. Chuy\u7879 n v\u7915 a r\u7891 i khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\'ec \u273 \u7893 i l\u7845 y an to\'e0n c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 b\'e1n m\'ecnh \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ch\'e1n n\u7843 n n\'e0y kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o b\u7897 c l\u7897 , d\'f9 sao chuy\u7879 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \'e3 v\u432 \u7907 t ra kh\u7887 i ph\u7841 m vi nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o \u273 em chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y t\'f9y ti\u7879 n n\'f3i cho b\u7841 n b\'e8 nghe, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o cam \u273 oan b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  tin c\u7853 u m\'e0 l\u7841 i lo l\u7855 ng cho r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u b\u7903 i v\'ec m\u7897 t m\'ecnh ra n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i ch\u432 a th\'edch \u7913 ng n\'ean m\u7899 i b\u7883  th\u7847 n kinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7853 m r\u7873  r\u7873  tr\u432 \u7907 t ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng ra, g\u7885 i cho m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7899 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t cu\u7897 c g\u7885 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ean kia r\uc0\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t m\'e1y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong \uc0\u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u7845 p \'fang k\u7875  l\u7841 i bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "R\uc0\u7845 t c\u417  tr\'ed \u273 \u7845 y." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe xong l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i, "C\u7853 u n\'f3i c\u7853 u gi\u7843  v\u7901  m\'ecnh l\'e0 t\'ecnh nh\'e2n c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \u7875  h\'f9 d\u7885 a nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia? C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 gi\u7843  l\'e0m t\'ecnh nh\'e2n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t \u7845 p a \u7845 p \'fang bi\u7879 n gi\u7843 i, "Ch\u7881  l\'e0, ch\u7881  l\'e0 gi\u7843  v\u7901  h\u7855 n c\'f3 s\u7921  ch\'fa \'fd \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t v\u7899 i em."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Vi\uc0\u7879 c n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\u7847 n sau b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i th\u7859 ng v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer vi\u7879 c nh\u7919 ng k\u7867  \u273 \'f3 l\'e0m. D\u7895  h\u7855 n vui v\u7867  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\u7871 u Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng s\u7861 n l\'f2ng v\'ec c\u7853 u m\'e0 \u273 \u7913 ng ra l\'e0m ch\u7911 , vi\u7879 c tr\u7915 ng tr\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  nhanh h\u417 n \u273 i t\'f4i t\u7889  gi\'e1c, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng s\u7869  c\'f2n x\u7917  n\u7863 ng h\u417 n. Ph\u7843 i xem c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7871  l\'e0m h\u7855 n vui v\u7867  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2u." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  n\'f3i, \'e2m cu\u7889 i uy\u7875 n chuy\u7875 n tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\u7841 i mang theo tho\'e1ng ch\'fat d\u7909  d\u7895  .\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh h\uc0\u7895 n \u273 \u7843 n." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7855 n r\u259 ng m\u7855 ng, "\u7902  \u273 \'e2u ra lo\u7841 i th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  nh\u432  anh h\u7843 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i k\'eau m\'ecnh \'96 m\u7897 t nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i, \u273 \'f2i l\u7841 i c\'f4ng b\u7857 ng cho b\u7843 n th\'e2n b\u7857 ng c\'e1ch \u273 i l\u7845 y l\'f2ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u? C\u361 ng ch\'ednh b\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng tin gi\u7889 ng anh n\'ean b\u7885 n Alex m\u7899 i d\'e1m x\u7857 ng b\u7853 y nh\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, l\'e0 t\'f4i kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, t\'f4i sai r\u7891 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng m\u7873 m gi\u7885 ng d\u7895  c\u7853 u, "\u272 \u7873 u l\'e0 t\'f4i kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng n\'ean n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n c\u7889  \'fd l\'e0m h\u7855 n vui v\u7867 , c\u7853 u l\'e0m c\'e1i g\'ec h\u7855 n c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u vui, c\u7853 u ch\u7883 u \u273 i g\u7863 p h\u7855 n \u273 \u7875  h\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 vui \u273 \u7871 n bay l\'ean tr\u7901 i r\u7891 i. Nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t nhi\'ean ta v\u7851 n r\u7845 t ch\u7901  mong \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\u7841 ng ngoan ngo\'e3n c\u7911 a em l\'fac c\u7889  \'fd d\u7895  ta vui v\u7867  l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o. C\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u7911 y khu\u7845 t kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng *\u273 \u7847 u ho\'e0i t\u7889 ng b\'e3o hay kh\'f4ng? Khi \u273 \'f3 b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\u7853 t s\u7921  s\u7869  vui \u273 \u7871 n bay l\'ean tr\u7901 i m\u7845 t.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (\uc0\u273 \u7847 u ho\'e0i t\u7889 ng b\'e3o: \'c1m ch\u7881  h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \'f4m \u7845 p y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng nh\u432 ng v\'ec m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch kh\'e1c.)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t mu\u7889 n nh\'ecn, ch\u7881  ngh\u297  t\u7899 i th\'f4i \u273 \'e3 c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i t\u7915  trong m\u7897 ng \u273 \u7865 p r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey tr\uc0\u7847 m m\u7863 c \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean, nh\'ecn Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean c\u7917 a s\u7893 , kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7897  ra n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 To\'e0n m\uc0\u7845 y c\'e2u v\u7899  v\u7849 n linh tinh. Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7845 t l\u7921 c \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i v\u7883  th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, em kh\'f4ng t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, em ch\u7881  l\'e0 hi v\u7885 ng th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  c\'e1c anh c\'f3 th\u7875  ki\'ean c\u432 \u7901 ng h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat." Kh\'f4ng th\u7875  b\u7903 i v\'ec Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer kia l\'e0 sinh v\u7853 t h\u7855 c \'e1m c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i g\'ec \u273 \'f3 m\'e0 li\u7873 n kinh s\u7907  ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7843 ng kho\'e1i l\'ean ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c chuy\u7875 n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7873 , "V\u7853 y v\u7915 a r\u7891 i r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\u7853 u v\'ec sao m\'e0 kh\u7893  s\u7903 ? Thanh \'e2m nghe v\'e0o l\u7841 i \u7911 y khu\u7845 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y. L\u7841 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i hay qu\u7927  n\'e0o khi d\u7877  c\u7853 u? Ch\u7885 c gi\u7853 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng vui? T\'f4i \u273 i gi\'e1o hu\u7845 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  thay c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai khi d\uc0\u7877  em c\u7843 ." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7889  \'fd n\'f3i, "Ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia."\cb1 \
\cb3 Anh c\'f3 d\'e1m \uc0\u273 i gi\'e1o hu\u7845 n h\u7855 n \u273 \'e2u, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t m\u7841 nh mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i su\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 m... V\'ec chuy\u7879 n h\u7855 n h\'f4n c\u7853 u l\'fac \u273 ang h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u m\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7915 a k\u7875  \'e0?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u259 m d\'f2 h\u7887 i, "A Di\'ean, c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i bi\u7871 t r\u7857 ng, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ngon mi\u7879 ng c\'f9ng lo\u7841 i d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng n\'e0y c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c g\u7855 n b\'f3 ch\u7863 t ch\u7869 , v\'ec v\u7853 y l\'fac \u7845 y c\'f3 l\u7869  h\u7855 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 qu\'e1 \u273 \'f3i kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  n\u7893 i b\u7843 n n\u259 ng n\'ean m\u7899 i l\'e0m v\u7853 y, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7889  \'fd m\u7841 o ph\u7841 m c\u7853 u. N\u7871 u nh\u432  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7883  m\u7841 o ph\u7841 m, t\'f4i xin l\u7895 i c\u7853 u thay h\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Em ph\uc0\u7843 i tin t\u432 \u7903 ng ta th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd m\u7841 o ph\u7841 m em, ta ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u273 \u417 n thu\u7847 n mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n em, mu\u7889 n ch\u7841 m v\'e0o em, mu\u7889 n h\'f4n em, mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 n em tri\u7879 t tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7875  tr\u7903  th\'e0nh c\u7911 a ta... Mu\u7889 n v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n nh\u7889 t em l\u7841 i trong l\'f2ng ta.\cb1 \
