\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7853 p tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a v\u7883  th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  n\'e0y c\u259 n b\u7843 n l\'e0 v\u7863 n v\u7865 o, th\u7871  m\'e0 l\u7841 i \u273 i xin l\u7895 i thay Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c? ! Hay l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7845 y b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 kho\'e1c l\'e1c n\'f3i ra mi\u7879 ng nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 i d\u7841 y d\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer n\'ean m\u7899 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  \u273 \u432 a ra bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p v\u7899  v\u7849 n "Xin l\u7895 i thay h\u7855 n" \u273 \u7875  an \u7911 i m\'ecnh?\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng th\'e8m \u273 \u7875  anh thay m\u7863 t. L\u7901 i xin l\u7895 i c\u7911 a anh h\u7855 n m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng th\'e8m th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  Di\u7879 p Tom c\'f3 t\u7845 m l\'f2ng nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh, b\u7909 ng d\u7841  ch\'e2n th\u7853 t, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, c\'f2n th\'edch m\u7841 nh mi\u7879 ng kho\'e1c l\'e1c. \u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u361 ng \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau, h\u417 n n\u7919 a th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c an \u7911 i m\u7897 t c\'e1ch k\u7923  l\u7841 , ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong l\'f2ng v\u7915 a \u7845 m v\u7915 a m\u7873 m, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\u7893  s\u7903  sau khi g\u7863 p Alex to\'e0n b\u7897  b\u7883  qu\'e9t s\u7841 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7843 m \u417 n anh, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Gi\u7901  em c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7889 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng kia \u273 \u7871 n h\'fat m\'e1u n\u7919 a em c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng s\u7907 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c t\'e1n g\u7851 u h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7845 y ch\u7911  \u273 \u7873  nh\'e0m ch\'e1n nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 \u259 n s\'e1ng ch\u432 a, t\u7889 i qua ng\u7911  c\'f3 ngon kh\'f4ng, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t ph\u432 \u417 ng, sau khi c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng v\u7851 n c\'f2n kh\u7869  cong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng anh nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng r\u7845 t \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n hy v\u7885 ng anh c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7903  n\'ean l\u7907 i h\u7841 i h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, tr\u7903  th\'e0nh m\u7897 t th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'f3 \'edch h\u417 n. C\u7853 u y\'ean l\u7863 ng n\'f3i trong l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  ngon, sau khi c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i n\u7857 m m\u7897 t m\'ecnh tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u417 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 ng\u7911 , m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u7903  ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a g\u7885 i c\u7853 u \u273 i \u259 n m\u7899 i d\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng h\'f4m nay Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n c\'f3 h\u417 i ch\u259 m ch\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng s\'e1ng Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u th\u7913 c d\u7853 y t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i tr\u7877 , nh\u432 ng h\'f4m nay ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n t\'e1m gi\u7901  h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c, l\'fac ng\u7911  l\u7841 i th\'ec c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n h\u7885 c b\'e0i, th\u7871  l\'e0 d\u7913 t kho\'e1t ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u n\u7845 u c\u417 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e0nh ph\uc0\u7889  Sophus kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, gi\'e1 c\u7843  l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7845 p, th\u7921 c ph\u7849 m c\u361 ng \u273 \u7855 t h\u417 n so v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng th\'e0nh ph\u7889  l\u7899 n nh\u432  Cairns v\'e0 Brisbane. So s\'e1nh m\'e0 n\'f3i, trong si\'eau th\u7883  \u7913 c g\'e0 l\'e0 nguy\'ean li\u7879 u \u273 \u7855 t nh\u7845 t \'97\'97 n\u417 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng v\u7899 i trong n\u432 \u7899 c, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 thi\'ean h\u432 \u7899 ng th\'edch \u7913 c g\'e0 h\u417 n; \u273 \'f9i g\'e0, c\'e1nh g\'e0 r\u7867  h\u417 n \u7913 c g\'e0; tim, m\u7873  g\'e0, c\u7893  g\'e0 m\u7845 y lo\u7841 i nguy\'ean li\u7879 u n\'e0y l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ai \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n hai ba \u273 \'f4 l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  mua m\u7897 t h\u7897 p, th\u7871  n\'ean m\u7845 y th\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng m\'f3n \u259 n hay \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Giang \u272 i\u7873 n bi\u7871 n \u273 \u7893 i \u273 a d\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\u7845 u s\u7889 t hai h\u7897 p c\u7893  g\'e0, kho m\u7897 t n\u7891 i c\'e1nh g\'e0, l\u7841 i d\'f9ng n\u432 \u7899 c th\u7883 t kho g\'e0 x\'e0o khoai t\'e2y, d\'f9ng b\u7897 t khoai lang b\'e1n trong si\'eau th\u7883  Trung Qu\u7889 c n\u7845 u m\u7897 t n\u7891 i s\'fap chua cay l\u7899 n, g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n trong nh\'f3m chat m\u7901 i m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n \u259 n. K\u7871 t qu\u7843  ch\u7881  c\'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843  bu\u7893 i kh\'f4ng h\u7891 i \'e2m tin nh\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e2u, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i t\u7921  m\'ecnh ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7885 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe n\'f3i c\'f3 c\uc0\u417 m \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean vui v\u7867 , d\u7909 i m\u7855 t r\u7917 a m\u7863 t xong li\u7873 n \u273 i theo.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7847 ng m\u7897 t k\'fd t\'fac c\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'e0 h\'e0ng b\'ecnh d\'e2n, ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  c\'e1c t\u7847 ng kh\'e1c nhau \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7885 n c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i \u259 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n kh\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n, l\'e3o Cao th\'e8m kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, ch\u432 a ch\u7901  b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e3 v\u7909 ng tr\u7897 m g\u7855 p m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c c\u7893  g\'e0 g\u7863 m \u259 n, sau khi th\u7845 y hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i t\u7899 i li\u7873 n v\u7897 i v\'e0ng nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng, gi\u7843  b\u7897  c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng ch\u432 a ph\'e1t sinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'e0n \u259 n, t\'e2m tr\u7841 ng v\u7889 n \u273 ang r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y l\'e3o Cao \u259 n v\u7909 ng c\u361 ng th\u7845 y vui, cho \u273 \u7871 n khi th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'e0n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i \'97\'97 ng\u7891 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh ch\'ednh l\'e0 Alex v\u7899 i \u273 \'e1m b\u7841 n h\u7855 n, ch\'ednh x\'e1c h\u417 n m\'e0 n\'f3i, l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  trong m\u7855 t b\u7885 n h\u7855 n, b\u7843 n th\'e2n nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y c\'f2n ngon mi\u7879 ng h\u417 n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n tr\'ean b\'e0n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Jody c\uc0\u361 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\'f4 \u7843  l\'f3e l\'ean, l\u7863 ng l\u7869  \u273 \u7909 ng \u273 \u7909 ng Alex, gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai h\u7855 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "N\'e0y, ti\u7875 u t\u7917  kia th\u7871  m\'e0 kh\'f4ng sao \'e0? Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i n\'f3i d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p cao c\'f2n th\u7883 nh h\u417 n sao? T\'f4i c\'f2n t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer s\u7869  h\'fat kh\'f4 c\u7853 u ta lu\'f4n ch\u7913 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex s\uc0\u7855 c m\u7863 t c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c, kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, Simon \u7903  b\'ean nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng nh\u7855 c: "Jody, kh\'f4ng n\'ean \u273 \'e0m lu\u7853 n chuy\u7879 n v\u7873  ng\u432 \u7901 i kia."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\'e1t sau Alex m\u7899 i nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng nh\u7855 c nh\u7903 : "Kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i Jerry s\u7869  t\u7889 t h\u417 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7891  v\u7899 i c\u7853 u ta n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Jody sau khi nghe xong nh\uc0\u7887  gi\u7885 ng o\'e1n tr\'e1ch m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "N\'e0y l\u7841 i l\'e0 t\u7841 i sao \u273 \'e2y? Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 quy \u273 \u7883 nh n\'e0o n\'f3i m\u7897 t khi Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 u\u7889 ng m\'e1u th\'ec s\u7869  kh\'f4ng cho Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'e1c u\u7889 ng n\u7919 a \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex kh\'f4ng gi\uc0\u7843 i th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean gi\u7843 i th\'edch th\u7871  n\'e0o, b\u7903 i v\'ec n\u7871 u mu\u7889 n gi\u7843 i th\'edch, l\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i ra n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng s\u7869  c\'f2n g\'e2y ra s\'f3ng gi\'f3 l\u7899 n h\u417 n so v\u7899 i h\u7855 n t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i g\'e2y phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c cho ch\'ednh h\u7855 n. H\u7855 n n\'ean n\'f3i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o? Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  n\'f3i, s\'e1ng h\'f4m nay t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y b\u7857 ng ch\u7913 ng, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \'e3 tham lam h\'f4n c\u7843  nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i kia? V\u7853 y ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n l\'e0 h\u7855 n \u273 i\'ean r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n bi\u7871 t tuy r\u7857 ng b\u7873  ngo\'e0i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i ngh\u7883  lu\u7853 n ra v\'e0o kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang v\u7873  nh\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p cao kia, nh\u432 ng tr\'ean th\u7921 c t\u7871  nh\'e2n v\u7853 t c\'e0ng l\u7899 n tin \u273 \u7891 n s\u7869  truy\u7873 n \u273 i c\'e0ng nhanh, hu\u7889 ng chi l\'e0 tin \u273 \u7891 n b\u7841 o t\u7841 c ph\'e1 v\u7905  h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7907 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng thay \u273 \u7893 i c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer th\u7847 n b\'ed nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'ec t\'ednh to\'e1n t\uc0\u7921  b\u7843 o v\u7879  m\'ecnh m\'e0 c\u7889  t\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  th\'f4ng tin \u273 \'e3 mang \u273 \u7871 n cho h\u7855 n ch\u7845 n \u273 \u7897 ng c\'f2n l\u7899 n h\u417 n h\u7855 n ngh\u297 . B\u7903 i trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7889  h\u7919 u c\u7911 a to\'e0n b\u7897  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer l\'e0 m\u7897 t s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\'e2n c\u7853 n v\u7899 i b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c ho\u7863 c nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i n\'e0o, th\u7853 m ch\'ed ngay c\u7843  u\u7889 ng m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i s\u7917  d\u7909 ng ly th\u7911 y tinh l\'e0m v\u7853 t ch\u7913 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng d\u7845 u v\u7871 t \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7911  \u273 \u7875  n\'f3i r\'f5 trong m\u7855 t Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, c\u7853 u ta so v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng g\'ec t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\'f2n \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t h\u417 n, c\'f2n ngo\u7841 i l\u7879  h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 Jody mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e1p \'e1n, Simon v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'e1c \u273 ang ng\u7891 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng r\u7845 t t\'f2 m\'f2 v\'ec sao Alex \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\'f3i v\u7853 y, nh\u432 ng b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\'f3i xa n\'f3i g\u7847 n th\u7871  n\'e0o, Alex c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\'f3i th\'eam m\u7897 t ch\u7919 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y Julia \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c s\'e2n \u273 i v\'e0o nh\'e0 h\'e0ng, n\'f3i v\u7899 i b\'e0n c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n: "Jerry, Jerry 407 \u7903  \u273 \'e2y ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 m\u7897 t v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh t\'f3c x\'e1m t\'ecm c\u7853 u, b\'e2y gi\u7901  \'f4ng \u7845 y \u273 ang \u7903  trong chi\u7871 c xe h\u417 i ngo\'e0i kia ch\u7901  c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\'ean sinh t\'f3c x\'e1m... Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong l\'f2ng c\u259 ng l\'ean, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 ai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nhanh qu\'e1 v\uc0\u7853 y? Th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n ch\u432 a qua 24 ti\u7871 ng, v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia \u273 \u7883 nh ba m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y m\u7895 i ng\'e0y m\u7895 i b\u7919 a \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng b\u7887  sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, kh\u7869  n\'e2ng gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\'e1m \u417 n v\u7899 i Julia: "C\u7843 m \u417 n ch\u7883  \u273 \'e3 b\'e1o cho em bi\u7871 t, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh h\'f4m qua \u273 \u432 a em v\u7873 . Em th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\u7897  y ph\u7909 c \u273 \u7875  s\'f3t \u7903  ch\u7895  em, ch\u7855 c \'f4ng \u7845 y bi\u7871 t ch\u7911  nh\'e2n b\u7897  y ph\u7909 c \u273 \'f3 n\'ean quay l\u7841 i l\u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 ang c\u7889  \'fd n\'f3i cho \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\'e0n \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n nghe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'f9ng d\uc0\u432  quang li\u7871 c qua th\u7845 y m\u7845 y qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia kh\u7869  gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 \u273 \'f4i khi r\u7845 t c\u7847 n nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  \u273 \u7891 ng t\'ecnh ho\u7863 c k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng t\u7915  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  ki\'ean tr\'ec l\'e0m m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c ho\u7863 c \u273 \'fang ho\u7863 c kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng nay trong \uc0\u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 t\'e1n d\u432 \u417 ng th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n ti ti\u7879 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, cho r\u7857 ng c\'e1ch n\'e0y h\u7919 u hi\u7879 u m\'e0 c\u417  tr\'ed, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7893  v\u361 , quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c gi\u7843  v\u7901  m\'ecnh v\'e0 v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  n\u7885  c\'f3 quan h\u7879  kh\'f4ng t\u7847 m th\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia tr\u432 \u7899 c khi b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\u7883  tr\u7915 ng ph\u7841 t. D\'f9 th\u7871  n\'e0o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927 , \'fd ki\u7871 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\'f3 l\u7869  v\u7851 n chuy\'ean nghi\u7879 p v\'e0 \u273 \'e1ng tin h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4ng b\'e1o xong li\u7873 n t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t b\u7841 n m\'ecnh r\u7891 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ch\u7841 y l\'ean t\u7847 ng l\u7845 y \'e1o kho\'e1c, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7847 m \'e1o v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ch\u7841 y ra ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 ang ng\u7891 i trong xe ch\u7901  c\u7853 u. L\'fac n\'e0y \u273 ang l\'e0 gi\u7919 a tr\u432 a, m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i Sophus \u273 \u7847 u th\'e1ng t\u432  v\u7851 n n\'f3ng r\u7921 c chi\u7871 u xu\u7889 ng, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'f3 l\u7869  r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng th\'edch n\u7855 ng g\u7855 t ch\'f3i chang nh\u432  v\u7853 y, Grey c\u361 ng th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 ch\'fat c\u7843 m th\'f4ng v\u7899 i v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xem ra b\uc0\u7845 t lu\u7853 n ch\u7911 ng t\u7897 c n\'e0o c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u gi\u7889 ng nhau, \u273 i l\'e0m c\'f4ng cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 tho\u7843 i m\'e1i d\u7877  ch\u7883 u. V\u7883  ti\'ean sinh Grey kia v\u7899 i t\u432  c\'e1ch m\u7897 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'f3 l\u7869  t\'ednh c\'e1ch tr\u7901 i sinh h\u7859 n l\'e0 th\'edch \u7849 n ng\'e0y xu\u7845 t \u273 \'eam, l\u7841 i v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng \u273 i mua \u273 \u7891  \u259 n cho \'f4ng ch\u7911  m\'ecnh ngay l\'fac gi\u7919 a tr\u432 a m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i tr\'ean \u273 \u7881 nh th\u7871  n\'e0y, ng\u7851 m ngh\u297  c\u361 ng th\u7845 y th\u7853 t c\u7921 c kh\u7893  m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean th\uc0\u7921 c t\u7871  m\u7897 t th\'e1ng sau khi c\'f9ng Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  \u273 \u7871 n Sophus, Grey \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n ra Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p, nh\u432 ng m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u \'f4ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, ch\u7881  cho l\'e0 \u273 \'fang l\'fac th\u7913 c t\u7881 nh t\u7915  trong l\'fac gi\u7845 c ng\u7911  say, kh\'f4ng th\'edch \u7913 ng v\u7899 i n\u7855 ng n\'f3ng c\u7911 a Sophus n\'ean Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng m\u7899 i kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chung quy khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  ch\u7881  th\'edch su\u7889 t ng\'e0y \'f4m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ng\u7891 i trong ph\'f2ng c\u432 \u7901 i t\u7911 m t\u7881 m, tuy r\u7857 ng th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i \'f4ng kh\'e1c m\u7897 t tr\u7901 i m\u7897 t v\u7921 c, song kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng ph\u7843 i xen v\'e0o.\cb1 \
