\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng v\u7873  sau \'f4ng m\u417  h\u7891  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c s\u7921  t\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 v\u432 \u7907 t kh\u7887 i t\u7847 m ki\u7875 m so\'e1t, sinh m\u7841 ng d\'e0i l\'e2u v\'e0 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c h\u7885 c t\u7853 p xu\u7845 t s\u7855 c c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c gi\'fap \'f4ng n\u7855 m gi\u7919  r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u k\u7929  n\u259 ng, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  \'f4ng c\u361 ng th\'f4ng hi\u7875 u ti\u7871 ng Trung, cho n\'ean th\u7853 t ra \'f4ng nghe hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7897 i dung nh\u7919 ng cu\u7897 c g\u7885 i c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 \'97\'97 b\'e2y gi\u7901  suy ngh\u297  l\u7841 i \'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7903 n gai \u7889 c, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tin \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i kia l\'e0 t\u7915  trong mi\u7879 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i ra, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tin \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  m\'e0 \'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 t\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng s\u7921  t\'ecnh qu\u7927  d\u7883  kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'ean \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7881 nh \u273 \'eam qua \'97\'97 \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  g\u7885 i \'f4ng mang nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i n\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n g\u7863 p ng\'e0i, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 a nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i n\'e0y c\'f9ng b\u7841 n c\u7853 u ta tr\u7903  v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \'f4ng ho\'e0n th\'e0nh nhi\uc0\u7879 m v\u7909  tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\u432  m\u7885 i ng\'e0y, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, \'f4ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c bi\u7871 t c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c \'97\'97 Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  \u273 \'e3 t\u7921  m\'ecnh h\'fat m\'e1u nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i. V\u7899 i t\u432  c\'e1ch m\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 t\u7891 n t\u7841 i h\u417 n m\u7897 t ngh\'ecn n\u259 m, \'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7909 c v\u7885 ng v\'e0 nhu c\u7847 u v\u7873  m\'e1u c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ngh\'ecn n\u259 m qua \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t nh\u7841 t, \'f4ng \'e2m th\u7847 m suy \u273 o\'e1n nguy\'ean nh\'e2n quan tr\u7885 ng nh\u7845 t trong \u273 \'f3 ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\u7921  m\'ecnh ti\u7871 p x\'fac c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7875  h\'fat m\'e1u. M\'e0 b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\u7841 i kh\'e1c, Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  ph\'e1 gi\u7899 i, s\u7869  r\u7845 t kh\'f3 h\u7891 i ph\u7909 c l\u7841 i tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i v\'f4 d\u7909 c v\'f4 c\u7847 u l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c. D\u7909 c v\u7885 ng nh\u432  h\u7891 ng th\u7911 y, m\u7897 t khi tr\'e0n ra, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7843 o d\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i tr\u432 a h\'f4m nay \'f4ng nh\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7879  d\'e2ng ly th\u7911 y tinh \u273 \u7921 ng m\'e1u cho Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \'f4\u803 ng \u273 \u7871 n ly m\'e1u n\u7885 . Th\u7901 i gian tr\'f4i qua, m\u7897 t gi\u7901  sau \'f4ng nh\u7853 n l\u7841 i ly th\u7911 y tinh m\'e1u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n t\u432 \u417 i nh\u432 ng ch\u432 a ch\u432 a h\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'f4\u803 ng \u273 \u7871 n, th\u7915 a c\u417  c\u7849 n th\u7853 n d\'f2 h\u7887 i c\'f3 mu\u7889 n t\'ecm m\u7897 t nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y hay kh\'f4ng, trong b\u7909 ng c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 \u273 \'e1p \'e1n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngo\'e0i s\uc0\u7903  li\u7879 u, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer bu\'f4ng cu\u7889 n s\'e1ch d\'e0y trong tay xu\u7889 ng, nh\'ecn qua phong c\u7843 nh n\u417 i xa ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 , v\u7867  nh\u432  y\'ean l\u7863 ng m\'e0 n\'f3i v\u7899 i \'f4ng: "\u272 i \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u ta t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y. Mang c\u7853 u ta \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean c\u7841 nh ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n x\'e1c nh\u7853 n hay h\u7887 i l\u7841 i, Grey \u273 \'e3 minh b\u7841 ch "C\u7853 u ta" l\'e0 ch\u7881  ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'ean l\'fac nh\uc0\u7853 n nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  \u273 i \u273 \'f3n ng\u432 \u7901 i \'f4ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7845 t ng\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng nh\'ecn nh\'e2n lo\uc0\u7841 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i c\u7847 m m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o quen thu\u7897 c trong tay ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 c\u7853 u k\u7929  c\'e0ng m\u7897 t phen, do d\u7921  n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n mang \'e1o \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i l\'e0 mu\uc0\u7889 n tr\u7843  l\u7841 i n\'f3 cho v\u7883 ... ti\'ean sinh kia." Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n." Grey suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\'f3i, "Nh\u432 ng n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i \u259 n m\u7863 c n\'f3 v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong c\'e2u \uc0\u273 \'f3, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7907 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \'f4ng li\u7873 n kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sophus d\'e2n s\uc0\u7889  kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m, t\u432 \u417 ng \u7913 ng theo \u273 \'f3 l\u432 \u7907 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0 xe c\u7897  \u273 i tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng r\u7845 t \'edt. Grey m\u7855 t s\u7855 c th\u7845 y tr\'ean ven ph\u7843 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  ng\'e3 d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t, d\u432 \u7899 i th\'e2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng \u273 \u7887  t\u432 \u417 i, v\u7871 t m\'e1u loang nhu\u7897 m \u273 \u7887  c\u7843  m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng nhanh ch\'f3ng d\uc0\u7915 ng xe b\'ean c\u7841 nh, \u273 i l\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "B\'e0 c\'f3 sao kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 c\u7847 n t\'f4i gi\'fap g\'ec kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  c\u7889  n\'e9n \u273 au m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u: "C\u7843 m \u417 n. T\'f4i b\u7883  t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 l\'e0m tr\u432 \u7907 t ch\'e2n, ch\'e2n b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ean \u273 \'f9i b\'e0 c\u361 ng l\u7897  ra ngo\'e0i, b\u7855 p ch\'e2n b\u7883  c\u7841 nh s\u7855 c c\u7911 a t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 c\u7913 a r\'e1ch, th\u7883 t h\u7903  ra ngo\'e0i, m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng ch\u7843 y, nh\'ecn qua v\'f4 c\'f9ng \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng xu\u7889 ng xe theo, c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7853 n t\'e2m nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nhi\uc0\u7873 u m\'e1u th\u7871  n\'e0y... Li\u7879 u ti\'ean sinh Grey c\'f3 b\u7883  \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi th\uc0\u7845 y mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng Grey kh\u7869  nh\'edu m\'e0y: "... Xem ra ph\u7843 i \u273 \u432 a b\'e0 \u273 i vi\u7879 n r\u7891 i. Ch\u7881  t\'f4i m\u7899 i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n g\u7847 n nh\u7845 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng \'f4ng \uc0\u273 ang lo v\u7873  chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'f9ng \'e1nh m\u7855 t lo l\u7855 ng nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'97\'97 ch\u7881  mong s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y \u273 i vi\u7879 n m\'e0 tr\'ec ho\'e3n qu\'e1 l\'e2u, c\u417  m\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \'f4ng thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i mang c\u7909 c c\u432 ng b\'e9 nh\u7887  c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  n\'e0y v\u7873 , \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 so \u273 o chuy\u7879 n \'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \'f3n ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7873  tr\u7877  \u273 \'e2u nh\u7881 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng l\uc0\u7841 i li\u7871 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean, quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh qu\u259 ng b\u7887  m\u7845 y suy ngh\u297  lo b\'f2 tr\u7855 ng r\u259 ng n\'e0y. Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  sau khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\'f3n \u273 i\u7875 m t\'e2m nho nh\u7887  c\u7911 a ng\'e0i h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  ch\u7859 ng th\'e8m \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t \u273 \u7871 n s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh m\u7899 i \u273 \'fang, ch\u7899  n\'f3i chi l\'e0 truy c\u7913 u chuy\u7879 n v\u7873  mu\u7897 n.\cb1 \
