\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i theo Grey \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng v\'e0o vi\u7879 n r\u7891 i m\u7899 i r\u7901 i \u273 i, m\'e1u ch\u7843 y t\u7915  mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0m d\u417  ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i ph\'eda sau.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Grey nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y nh\'edu nh\'edu m\'e0y, l\u7849 m b\u7849 m: "Ph\u7843 i nhanh \u273 i \u273 \u7893 i m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7887 i ra nghi v\u7845 n trong l\'f2ng: "\'d4ng c\'f3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4g? Sao m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng g\'ec v\u7899 i \'f4ng? C\'f2n... ra tay gi\'fap ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey k\uc0\u7923  qu\'e1i li\u7871 c c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  c\u7853 u tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u7891  \u259 n li\u7873 n nh\'e0o t\u7899 i sao? H\u417 n n\u7919 a t\u7841 m th\u7901 i ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i v\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 lo\u7841 i quan h\u7879  g\'ec, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng c\u361 ng s\u7869  ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7913 u ch\u7919 a, \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c v\'e0 nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i ch\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  h\u417 i kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t \u7903  c\'e1ch th\u7913 c sinh t\u7891 n v\'e0 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c h\'e0nh vi, b\u7873  ngo\'e0i, tr\'ed n\u259 ng v\'e0 ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c t\u432  duy \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t gi\u7889 ng nhau, sinh ra l\'f2ng c\u7843 m th\'f4ng v\'e0 quan t\'e2m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n r\u7845 t b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'f3i r\u7845 t c\'f3 l\'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\u7845 y qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\'ean c\u7841 nh t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u d\'f9ng th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n l\u7915 a g\u7841 t \u273 \u7875  h\'fat m\'e1u, n\'f3i chi l\'e0 \u273 \u7891  \u259 n d\'e2ng t\u7899 i c\u7917 a." Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\'c0," Grey gi\uc0\u7877 u c\u7907 t kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, "L\u7841 i l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i kh\'f4ng tu\'e2n theo quy c\u7911 . Tr\u432 \u7903 ng l\'e3o h\u7897 i ch\'e2u \'c2u \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m th\'f4ng qua quy \u273 \u7883 nh tr\u7909 c xu\u7845 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i kh\'f4ng tu\'e2n quy c\u7911  ra kh\u7887 i t\u7897 c, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  b\u7883  th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7843 n. C\u361 ng ch\u7881  \u7903  ch\'e2u \'dac b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7899 i d\'e1m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\u417 n n\u7919 a t\'f4i nghe n\'f3i n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y th\u7907  s\u259 n v\'e0 khu ma s\u432  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t l\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e1c."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (khu ma s\uc0\u432 : th\u7847 y tr\u7915  ma t\'e0)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Grey v\uc0\u7915 a l\'e1i xe v\u7915 a ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c gi\u7843 i th\'edch: "Qu\'fd t\u7897 c trong Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t danh hi\u7879 u m\'e0 quan tr\u7885 ng h\u417 n l\'e0 m\u7863 t kia c\u7911 a ph\u7847 n vinh d\u7921  n\'e0y, \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7843 m nh\u7853 n tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m v\'e0 gi\u7919  v\u7919 ng nguy\'ean t\u7855 c, h\u417 n n\u7919 a danh hi\u7879 u n\'e0y c\'f2n ng\u7847 m n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c cao qu\'fd h\u417 n\'97\'97 \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n l\u7915 a g\u7841 t hay \'e9p bu\u7897 c \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m vi\u7879 c; kh\'f4ng \u7913 c hi\u7871 p nh\u7887  y\u7871 u; trung th\'e0nh; th\u7911  t\'edn... \u272 \'e1ng ti\u7871 c b\'e2y gi\u7901  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y ng\'e0y c\'e0ng \'edt."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 m ch\'ed ngay c\u7843  \'f4ng h\u7847 u h\u7841  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  c\u361 ng vi ph\u7841 m v\'e0i nguy\'ean t\u7855 c trong \u273 \'f3. \'d4ng li\u7871 c nh\'ecn nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh \'97\'97 th\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  "Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n l\u7915 a g\u7841 t \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m vi\u7879 c" . Nh\u432 ng trong t\'edn \u273 i\u7873 u nh\'e2n sinh c\u7911 a \'f4ng, ph\u7909 c t\'f9ng v\'e0 trung th\'e0nh l\'e0 quy t\u7855 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u432 u ti\'ean h\u417 n so v\u7899 i n\'f3i ra s\u7921  th\u7853 t, cho n\'ean \'f4ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i n\'f3i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh th\u7921 c t\u7871  v\u7899 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng cho r\uc0\u7857 ng m\'ecnh n\u7871 u c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7853 n kh\u7843  n\u259 ng kh\'f4ng gi\'fap Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  \u273 i l\u7915 a b\u7883 p n\'f3i x\u7841 o l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t xu\u7845 t s\u7855 c r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ti\'ean sinh qu\u7843 n gia c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 d\u7921  c\u7843 m h\'f4m nay vi\u7879 c l\'e0m c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  qu\u7843  th\u7921 c nh\u432  ch\u417 i v\u7899 i l\u7917 a, chung quy s\u7869  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y b\u7841 i l\u7897 \'97\'97 l\u7901 i n\'f3i d\u7889 i kia qu\u7843  th\u7853 t qu\'e1 kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng tin c\u7853 y, v\'ec v\u7853 y \'f4ng hy v\u7885 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\'f3 th\u7875  \'e2m th\u7847 m n\'e2ng cao h\u7843 o c\u7843 m c\u7911 a nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. Tuy r\u7857 ng nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  n\'e0y nghe v\'e0o tai c\u361 ng h\u417 i kh\'f3 kh\u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\'e0i c\uc0\u361 ng l\'e0 qu\'fd t\u7897 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7887 i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng t\u7841 i sao \'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\'f4n s\'f9ng qu\'fd t\u7897 c qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u nh\u432  v\u7853 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i " Grey h\u417 i th\u7859 ng l\u432 ng l\'ean, "Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 t\'f4i l\'e0 qu\u7843 n gia \u432 u t\'fa, t\'f4n qu\'fd m\'e0 truy\u7873 n th\u7915 a l\'e2u \u273 \u7901 i c\u7911 a Emmer Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng, ngh\'ecn n\u259 m qua c\u361 ng v\u7851 n lu\'f4n k\u7871  th\u7915 a truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng quang vinh t\u7915  th\u7901 i xa x\u432 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Ti\'ean sinh Grey, t\'f4i mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i ng\'e0i m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , n\u7871 u m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i Alex l\'e0m th\u7871  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng tu\'e2n theo quy \u273 \u7883 nh, v\u7853 y b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\'f9ng c\'e1ch g\'ec \u273 \u7875  l\u7845 y m\'e1u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i ngh\uc0\u297  c\u7853 u c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i bi\u7871 t r\'f5 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 o l\'fd, " Grey kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m \u273 \'e1p, "D\u432 \u7899 i \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, tr\'ean th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y, t\'e0i nguy\'ean c\u7911 a t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c gi\u7889 ng lo\'e0i, c\u7911 a t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c h\'ecnh th\'e1i x\'e3 h\u7897 i g\u7847 n nh\u432  \u273 \u7873 u ph\'e2n ph\u7889 i kh\'f4ng c\'f4ng b\u7857 ng tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i m\'e0 c\'f3 s\u7921  ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u361 ng v\u7853 y. M\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\u7877  l\u7845 y nh\u7845 t, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  h\'fat m\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7895 i ng\'e0y, ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7873 u h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y, nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  mua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7883 t t\u432 \u417 i \u7903  si\'eau th\u7883 , Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch duy tr\'ec v\'e0 mua b\'e1n m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ngo\'e0i ra, \uc0\u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\'e0 n\'f3i m\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i h\'e0ng ho\'e1, c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  mua b\'e1n, t\'f4i bi\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u v\u7873  m\u7863 t lu\'e2n l\'fd v\'e0 \u273 \u7841 o \u273 \u7913 c \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ch\'fang t\'f4i m\'e0 n\'f3i l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean, t\u7915  x\u432 a \u273 \'e3 ch\'ednh l\'e0 nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia tr\'ecnh \u273 \u7897  s\u7913 c s\u7843 n xu\u7845 t c\u7911 a nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i th\u7845 p, chi\u7871 n tranh, thi\'ean tai, d\u7883 ch b\u7879 nh \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  g\'e2y kh\'f3 kh\u259 n cho s\u7921  sinh t\u7891 n c\u7911 a nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i, gi\'e1o h\u7897 i v\'e0 ch\'ednh quy\u7873 n th\u7901 i Trung C\u7893  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'f2n t\'e0n nh\u7851 n h\u417 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n h\u7847 u h\u7841  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'f3 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c, th\'f4ng qua b\'e1n m\'e1u m\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7893 i l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n s\u7889 ng \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh sung t\'fac h\u417 n. C\'e1ch l\'e0m nh\u432  v\u7853 y ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n theo l\u7883 ch s\u7917  cho t\u7899 i b\'e2y gi\u7901 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Hi\uc0\u7879 n gi\u7901  ch\'fang t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i r\'f5 \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n v\'e0 m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch v\u7899 i m\u7897 t s\u7889  nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  mua m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i c\u7911 a h\u7885 , \u273 a ph\u7847 n kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i kh\'f3 ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n vi\u7879 c b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p, c\'f3 th\u7875  d\'f9ng c\'e1ch t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921  nh\u432  hi\u7871 n m\'e1u \u273 \u7875  l\u7845 y m\'e1u r\u7891 i \u273 \u7921 ng v\'e0o v\u7853 t ch\u7913 a \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c s\u7869  d\'f9ng c\'e1ch th\u7913 c \u273 \u7863 c th\'f9 \u273 \u7875  gi\u7919  g\'ecn, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean th\u7901 i gian b\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 m ch\u7845 t l\u432 \u7907 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e0i; tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p d\'f9ng r\u259 ng h\'fat m\'e1u v\u7851 n l\'e0 ngon nh\u7845 t, t\u7845 t nhi\'ean nh\u432  v\u7853 y gi\'e1 c\u361 ng cao h\u417 n. Th\u7901 i \u273 \u7841 i ng\'e0y nay c\'f2n coi tr\u7885 ng h\u7907 p \u273 \u7891 ng, ch\'fang t\'f4i c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  k\'fd h\u7907 p \u273 \u7891 ng v\u7899 i 'Nh\'e0' cung c\u226 \u769 p, n\u7871 u l\'e0 h\u7907 p t\'e1c ng\u7855 n h\u7841 n th\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  ghi ch\'fa r\'f5 trong h\u7907 p \u273 \u7891 ng sau khi k\u7871 t th\'fac h\u7907 p t\'e1c s\u7869  ti\'eau tr\u7915  to\'e0n b\u7897  tr\'ed nh\u7899  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Hi\uc0\u7879 n gi\u7901  t\'f4i c\u361 ng coi nh\u432  l\'e0 'Nh\'e0 cung c\u226 \u769 p' ng\u7855 n h\u7841 n c\u7911 a c\'e1c \'f4ng?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i cau m\'e0y, m\u7863 c d\'f9 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch nh\u432  th\u7871 , c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u v\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\'f4 l\u7921 c khi b\u7883  \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'e0y l\u7915 a g\u7841 t uy hi\u7871 p. D\'f9 sao ngay t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n \u273 \u7875  b\u7845 t k\'ec con qu\u7927  n\'e0o h\'fat m\'e1u, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i \u273 \u7841 t th\'e0nh m\u7897 t \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\u7899 i v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey li\uc0\u7871 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "... Kh\'f4ng, ng\'e0i h\u7859 n l\'e0 xem nh\u432  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i duy nh\u7845 t Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  ch\u7881  \u273 \u7883 nh h\u7907 p t\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe d\uc0\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t trang vi\'ean \u7903  ngo\u7841 i th\'e0nh, n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y c\'f2n xa h\u417 n y\u7871 n h\u7897 i t\u7889 i qua, h\u432 \u7899 ng c\u361 ng ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i, xung quanh kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, trong t\u7847 m m\u7855 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y t\'f2a nh\'e0 hay h\u7897  gia \u273 \'ecnh n\'e0o kh\'e1c, y h\u7879 t nh\u7919 ng kh\'e1ch s\u7841 n ho\u7863 c c\u259 n nh\'e0 ma qu\'e1i m\'e0 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  c\u7847 u xin s\u7921  gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i trong phim kinh d\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Song Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m bi\u7871 t n\u417 i n\'e0y x\'e1c th\u7921 c c\'f3 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u361 ng s\u7899 m hi\u7875 u r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n, t\u7915  l\'fac l\'ean xe \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh ph\u7843 i \u273 i l\'e0m g\'ec, cho n\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m m\u7845 y tr\'f2 gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a v\'f4 v\u7883 , r\u7845 t th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n theo s\'e1t Grey \u273 i v\'e0o c\u7893 ng l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 trong ng\u7921 c v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng. L\u7847 n th\u7913  nh\u7845 t b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean x\u7843 y ra d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng d\u7921  li\u7879 u tr\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7853 t s\u7921  b\u7845 t ng\u7901  kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng. L\u7847 n th\u7913  hai b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u t\'e2m t\'e2m ni\u7879 m ni\u7879 m mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n Giang \u272 i\u7873 n c\'f9ng nhau an to\'e0n r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng lo l\u7855 ng s\u7907  h\'e3i. Hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  tuy \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 hai l\u7847 n kinh nghi\u7879 m, nh\u432 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n s\u7855 p t\u7899 i v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 \u273 \u7893  m\u7891  h\'f4i l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay, l\u432 ng ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 ch\'ednh l\'e0... l\'fac h\'fat m\'e1u r\u259 ng nanh c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng s\u7869  ho\'e0n to\'e0n ng\u7853 p v\'e0o trong c\u7893  m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i v\u7899 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i m\'e0 n\'f3i, c\u7893  \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng \u273 i\u7875 m y\u7871 u y\u7871 u \u7899 t nh\u7845 t ch\'ed m\u7841 ng nh\u7845 t. C\u7853 u theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7907  h\'e3i vi\u7879 c b\u7841 i l\u7897  ph\u7847 n c\u7893  tr\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867  \u273 i s\u259 n kh\'e1c, \u273 \u7875  h\u7855 n d\'f9ng r\u259 ng nanh m\u7863 c \'fd chi\u7871 m c\u7913  ph\u7847 n l\'e3nh \u273 \u7883 a n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a m\u7897 t c\u259 n ph\'f2ng \u7903  t\u7847 ng hai nh\u432  l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, sau khi nh\'ecn ch\'ednh c\u7853 u ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7847 m m\u7843 nh l\u7909 a \u273 en tr\'ean tay c\u7847 m c\u7917 a bu\u7897 c ch\u7863 t l\'ean m\u7855 t m\'ecnh th\'ec r\u7901 i \u273 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 o\'e1n \'f4ng \u273 ang v\u7897 i \u273 i r\u7917 a s\u7841 ch xe c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  t\'f2a nh\'e0 r\u7845 t y\'ean t\u297 nh, m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\'e1c thi\u7871 t b\u7883  v\'e0 b\'e0i tr\'ed trong nh\'e0 to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n m\'e0 hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7841 i, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  Grey ra th\'ec kh\'f4ng h\u7873  th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m kh\'e1c, kh\'e1c m\u7897 t tr\u7901 i m\u7897 t v\u7921 c v\u7899 i l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i c\u7893  c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u hay th\u7845 y trong phim, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c nh\u432  ch\u7911  nh\'e2n kh\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u n\u7919 a, \'f4m \'fd ngh\u297  ch\u7871 t s\u7899 m \u273 \u7847 u thai s\u7899 m, c\u7855 n r\u259 ng \u273 \u7849 y c\'e1nh c\u7917 a kh\'e9p h\u7901  ra \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 ang l\'e0 x\u7871  chi\u7873 u, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c t\u7889 i h\'f4m qua l\u7855 m\'97\'97 t\u7847 m m\u7855 t v\u7851 n \u273 en k\u7883 t nh\u432  c\u361 , tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t c\u361 ng ph\u7911  th\u7843 m d\'e0y l\'e0m c\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Trong ph\'f2ng \'e1nh s\'e1ng c\'f3 h\u7841 n, tr\'ean th\u7921 c t\u7871  c\u7843  t\'f2a nh\'e0 n\'e0y l\'fac thi\u7871 t k\u7871  l\'fac \u273 \'e3 c\u7889  t\'ecnh tr\'e1nh \'e1nh m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i, khi\u7871 n cho l\'fac gi\u7919 a tr\u432 a t\'f2a nh\'e0 c\u361 ng c\'f3 v\u7867  \'e2m u, thuy\u7871 t minh cho vi\u7879 c ngay t\u7915  l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t "Qu\u7927  tr\u7841 ch" \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thi\u7871 t k\u7871  cho qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe th\uc0\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng kh\'f3a c\u7917 a "C\u7841 ch" r\u7845 t nh\u7887 , bi\u7871 t ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 m\u7897 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u quen thu\u7897 c \u273 ang \u273 \u7907 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u \u273 ang ngh\u297  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u7907 t c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay thon d\'e0i h\u417 i l\u7841 nh n\u7855 m l\u7845 y tay m\'ecnh, d\u7855 t c\u7853 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i v\'e0o trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0n tay n\'e0y hi\uc0\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng xa l\u7841  g\'ec, d\'f9 sao \u273 \'eam qua c\'f2n ti\u7871 p x\'fac th\'e2n m\u7853 t v\u7899 i n\'f3. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t n\'f3 thu\u7897 c v\u7873  v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u d\u7855 t c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t ch\u7895  th\'ec d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7847 n m\'f2 v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, ch\u7841 m t\u7899 i m\u7897 t v\u7853 t c\u7913 ng b\u7857 ng g\u7895 . C\u7853 u \u273 o\'e1n ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'ecnh l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e1i b\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c t\u7915  ph\'eda sau \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n c\u7853 u. Qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \'f4m c\u7893  c\u7853 u, h\u417 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u, h\u417 i th\u7903  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o ph\u7843  tr\'ean g\'e1y c\u7853 u: "H\'ecnh nh\u432  ng\u432 \u417 i r\u7845 t c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng? C\'f3 v\u7867  c\'f2n c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng h\u417 n \u273 \'eam qua?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3." Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c ph\u7911  nh\u7853 n, c\u7853 u h\'edt m\u7897 t h\u417 i th\u7853 t s\'e2u, tho\'e1ng mang ch\'fat kh\u7849 n c\u7847 u, "Xin ng\'e0i... nhanh m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng n\'ean treo c\uc0\u7853 u n\u7917 a v\u7901 i \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y, \u273 \'f9a b\u7905 n c\u7853 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869 , sau \u273 \'f3 l\'e0n da ph\u7847 n g\'e1y b\'ean tr\'e1i c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c li\u7871 m l\'e1p l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o m\'e0 \u432 \u7899 t \'e1t. Hai tay c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng n\u7855 m th\'e0nh quy\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 t c\u7913 ng s\u7855 c nh\u7885 n quen thu\u7897 c \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean da, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ch\u7907 t \u273 au nh\'f3i, ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c t\'ea m\u7887 i quen thu\u7897 c qu\'e9t s\u7841 ch to\'e0n th\'e2n, hai ch\'e2n c\u7853 u m\u7873 m nh\u361 n, c\u417  th\u7875  kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\'e3 s\u7845 p v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, ch\u7881  d\u7921 a v\'e0o hai c\'e1nh tay c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ch\u7889 ng tr\'ean m\'e9p b\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y l\'e0 g\'e1y b\u7883  r\u259 ng c\u7855 m v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1nh tay Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c giam ch\u7863 t eo c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7875  n\u7917 a ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean c\u7911 a c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng b\'e0n. C\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 ang tho\u7843 i m\'e1i \u259 n u\u7889 ng c\u361 ng theo c\u7853 u th\u7843  th\u7845 p tr\u7885 ng t\'e2m, r\u259 ng nanh theo s\'e1t kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng m\'e0 kh\'f3a ph\u7847 n c\u7893  c\u7853 u, th\'e2n th\u7875  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7903 i v\'ec tr\u7885 ng t\'e2m thay \u273 \u7893 i m\'e0 tr\u7903  th\'e0nh d\'e1n v\'e0o c\'e0ng th\'eam g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y l\'e0 x\uc0\u7871  chi\u7873 u, \u273 a s\u7889  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang l\'e0m vi\u7879 c \u273 i h\u7885 c ho\u7863 c ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i. Tinh th\u7847 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng th\'eam \u273 \u7847 y, c\u361 ng c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n c\'e0ng th\'eam r\'f5 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u. C\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd c\u7911 a m\'ecnh t\u259 ng l\'ean cao \u273 \u7897 , to\'e0n b\u7897  t\u7853 p trung \u7903  nh\u7845 t c\u7917  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u sau l\u432 ng kia, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7843  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\u7889 c, l\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh nh\u432  l\u417  l\u7917 ng tr\'ean ch\'edn t\u7847 ng m\'e2y, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  m\u7895 i ph\'fat m\u7895 i gi\'e2y \u273 \u7873 u \u273 ang \u273 i tr\'ean m\'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  m\'e1u m\'ecnh ch\u7843 y h\'ecnh nh\u432  ch\u7853 m l\u7841 i, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\u7921 c k\u7923  h\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7909  qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh h\'fat m\'e1u, sau \u273 \'f3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915 ng ng\u7909 m t\u7915 ng ng\u7909 m t\u7915 ng ch\'fat t\u7915 ng ch\'fat ch\u7853 m r\'e3i th\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7913 c m\'e1u c\u7853 u, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p kh\'f4ng r\'fat r\u259 ng nh\u7885 n ra, d\'f9ng c\'e1ch n\'e0y k\'e9o d\'e0i th\u7901 i gian h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ki\'ean tr\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, l\u7847 n th\u7913  hai b\u7883  lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c khi\'eau chi\u7871 n c\u7921 c h\u7841 n c\'e1 nh\'e2n d\u7891 n \'e9p \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f3c l\'ean, m\u7899 i m\'f4ng lung c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng v\u7851 n ch\u432 a th\u7887 a m\'e3n r\'fat r\u259 ng nanh ra, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  hai l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c v\'ec c\u7853 u m\'e0 c\u7849 n th\u7853 n li\u7871 m mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 To\'e0n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\uc0\u7913 c, \'fd th\u7913 c c\u7853 u ng\'e2y ng\u7845 t, ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n c\u7913  n\u7857 m tr\'ean b\'e0n nh\u432  v\u7853 y ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i ch\u7889 c l\'e1t, nh\u432 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\u7841 i b\u7871  c\u7853 u l\'ean, \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7873 m m\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u417  th\u7875  tinh th\u7847 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 m\u7879 t m\u7887 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, l\u7841 i nh\u432  c\u361  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c\'97\'97 t\'ean Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  n\'e0y ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  ch\u432 a \u259 n no, mu\u7889 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u259 n th\'eam nh\u432  l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7901 i \u273 \u7845 t ch\u7913 ng gi\'e1m, c\u7853 u th\u7873  l\u7847 n n\'e0y b\u7843 n th\'e2n tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'e0m ra b\u7845 t k\u7923  \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c g\'ec h\u7845 p d\u7851 n h\u7855 n \u259 n m\'f3n th\u7913  hai.\cb1 \
