\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e1i g\'ec c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 ang \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng b\u7895 ng nh\'fac nh\'edch y\u7871 t h\u7847 u, do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, v\u7851 n thu\u7853 n theo n\'e2ng c\u7893  l\'ean. C\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u run r\u7845 t kh\u7869 , n\'f3i th\u7853 t, c\u7853 u r\u7845 t s\u7907 , t\u7915  \u273 \'eam qua \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u ba l\u432 \u7907 t, c\u7853 u lo l\u7855 ng cho m\'ecnh s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "S\uc0\u7907  h\'e3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y..." C\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y ph\'eda tr\'ean truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng th\u7903  d\'e0i l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i do l\u7895 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u hay kh\'f4ng, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u mang theo ch\'fat ti\u7871 u \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 i th\u7903  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'e1ch c\u7853 u c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng r\u259 ng nanh v\'e0 \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n trong d\u7921  \u273 o\'e1n nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, tr\'e1i l\u7841 i, m\u7897 t th\u7913  l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh m\u7873 m m\u7841 i d\'e1n l\'ean m\'f4i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i \u273 o\'e1n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 v\u7853 t g\'ec, v\'f4 th\u7913 c t\'f2 m\'f2 du\u7895 i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m li\u7871 m.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 M\uc0\u7873 m m\u7873 m, h\u417 i kh\'f4 h\u417 n \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i, mang theo \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\'e2n r\u7845 t nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0, m\'f4i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c... Trong ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u c\u7843  kinh, c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, c\'e1nh m\'f4i \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng thu\u7853 n th\u7871  c\u7841 y m\u7903 , l\u432 \u7905 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c du\u7895 i v\'e0o, c\'f3 ch\u7845 t l\u7887 ng theo \u273 \'f3 tr\'f4i v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng, qua v\'e0i gi\'e2y m\u7899 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'fat cho c\u7853 u h\u7859 n l\'e0... n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t? C\u7853 u ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng \u273 \'f4i y\'eau \u273 \u432 \u417 ng cu\u7891 ng nhi\u7879 t trong l\'fac h\'f4n nhau c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t c\u7911 a nhau, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  ra t\u7841 i sao Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c n\'e0y ph\u7843 i l\'e0m nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean, kh\'e1ng c\u7921  nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u v\u7873  b\'ean tr\'e1i, n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c c\u432 \u7905 ng \'e9p \u273 \'fat v\'e0o c\u7853 u ng\u7853 m trong mi\u7879 ng kh\'f4ng nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  canh l\'fac nh\u7893  ra, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n t\u7889 n c\'f4ng du\u7895 i l\u432 \u7905 i ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u273 u\u7893 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i. D\'f9 sao l\u7899 n \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901 , c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7909 ng ch\u7841 m qua n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, ch\u7899  n\'f3i chi l\'e0 nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, t\'e1ch kh\u7887 i c\u7853 u, ng\u7891 i th\u7859 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, sau \u273 \'f3 d\'f9ng m\u7897 t ng\'f3n tay v\'f3i v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \u273 \'e8 l\u7841 i l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, b\u7855 t bu\u7897 c c\u7853 u nu\u7889 t to\'e0n b\u7897  n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'e0y c\uc0\u361 ng qu\'e1 kh\'f4ng t\'f4n tr\u7885 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i. T\u7909 c ng\u7919  n\'f3i t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7845 t c\'f2n c\'f3 ba ph\u7847 n t\'ednh \u273 \u7845 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y m\u7897 t m\u7921 c ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng, nh\u432 ng hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i \u273 \u7871 n t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c n\u7893 i \u273 i\'ean, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p hung h\u259 ng d\'f9ng s\u7913 c c\u7855 n ng\'f3n tay trong mi\u7879 ng kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng b\u7883  c\u7853 u c\u7855 n, thanh \'e2m v\u7851 n l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m nh\u432  c\u361 , nghe kh\'f4ng ra n\u7917 a \u273 i\u7875 m t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, ch\u7881  y\'ean l\u7863 ng m\'e0 n\'f3i s\u7921  th\u7853 t: "Ng\u432 \u417 i ngoan ngo\'e3n nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng, d\u7883 ch th\u7875  c\u7911 a ta c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7907  gi\'fap th\'e2n th\u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i nhanh ch\'f3ng kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u li\'ean t\u7909 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y ta e ng\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7919 ng s\u7901 , h\'e0m r\u259 ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng m\u7845 y ph\u7847 n l\u7921 c. C\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i Grey \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng d\'f9ng n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t c\u7911 a \'f4ng \u273 \u7875  gi\'fap Giang \u272 i\u7873 n kh\'e9p mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a khi \u273 \'f3 \'f4ng c\'f2n n\'f3i l\'e0 d\u7883 ch th\u7875  c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p cao c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  ch\u7919 a tr\u7883  t\u7889 t h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'ec ra \uc0\u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t t\u7915  h\u7843 o \'fd. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ngang ng\u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng n\'f3i \u273 \u7841 o l\'fd, n\u7917 a b\u7913 c hi\u7871 p m\'ecnh l\u7853 p th\'e0nh \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh c\u361 ng l\'e0 h\u7855 n, h\'fat m\'e1u m\'ecnh c\u361 ng l\'e0 h\u7855 n, vi\u7879 c l\'e0m n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  x\u432 ng l\'e0 vi\u7879 c thi\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\'f3n tay b\u7883  m\'ecnh c\u7855 n v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u7903  trong mi\u7879 ng m\'ecnh, ch\u7911  nh\'e2n c\u7911 a n\'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7915 a c\u417  m\'e0 thu v\u7873 . Trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3 t\u432  duy Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat \u273 \'ecnh tr\u7879 , nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao, v\'f4 th\u7913 c l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n c\'e1ch d\'f9ng \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i \u273 u\u7893 i v\u7883  kh\'e1ch kh\'f4ng m\u7901 i m\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n n\'e0y ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7841 i ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  ng\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7919 ng s\u7901 , b\u7845 y gi\u7901  m\u7899 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p v\u7915 a r\u7891 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m g\'ec, kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7845 y tay che k\'edn m\u7863 t \'97\'97c\'e1ch l\'e0m v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 qu\'e1 ngu ng\u7889 c, th\u7875  di\u7879 n m\u7863 t m\u361 i v\u7913 t h\u7871 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t ch\u7911 ng t\u7897 c kh\'e1c r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u t\u7921 a h\u7891  th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean, ch\u7881  m\u7845 y gi\'e2y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c s\u7913 c l\u7921 c v\'e0 tinh th\u7847 n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u. C\u7853 u l\u7847 n m\'f2 b\'f2 d\u7853 y, "Nh\'ecn" v\u7873  n\u417 i ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i: "... B\'e2y gi\u7901  t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7921 a theo l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i, v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer n\'e0y c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t nh\'e2n v\u7853 t l\u7899 n trong Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\u7853 t l\u7885 ng, t\u7841 m th\u7901 i c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\u7847 n nh\u7851 n n\u7841 i th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n xong \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh ba m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y n\'e0y, sau \u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m kh\'f3 c\u7853 u n\u7919 a. M\'e0 ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  tin t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'e1c t\u7889 t h\u417 n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  b\u7843 n th\'e2n ph\u7843 i ki\'ean tr\'ec nh\u7851 n n\u7841 i \'97\'97 ch\u7881  mong l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 th\u7853 t, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer s\u7869  gi\u7919  l\u7901 i m\'e0 bu\'f4ng tha m\'ecnh, b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u li\'ean t\u7909 c c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\u432 u l\u7841 i di ch\u7913 ng g\'ec cho m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng s\u7921  ki\u7879 n li\'ean ti\u7871 p ph\'e1t sinh xung k\'edch to\'e0n b\u7897  th\u7871  gi\u7899 i quan khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u tr\u7903  tay kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  \u273 \u7897 ng \u7913 ng \u273 \u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7902  l\u7841 i \u259 n t\u7889 i." Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c y\'ean l\u7863 ng n\'f3i, "B\'e2y gi\u7901  ng\u432 \u417 i c\u7847 n ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i, ng\u7911  m\u7897 t l\'fac \u273 i, \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  c\u417 m t\u7889 i ta s\u7869  g\u7885 i ng\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'f2ng run s\uc0\u7907  m\'e0 suy ngh\u297  h\'e0m ngh\u297 a c\u7911 a c\'e2u "\u7902  l\u7841 i \u259 n c\u417 m t\u7889 i" n\u7885 , c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'e0y ph\'e1t h\u7843 o t\'e2m mu\u7889 n m\u7901 i m\'ecnh \u259 n c\u417 m, \'fd h\u7855 n ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 gi\u7919  m\'ecnh l\u7841 i l\'e0m b\u7919 a t\u7889 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y hai b\u7919 a m\u7895 i b\u7919 a \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng b\u7887  sao? C\'f3 ph\u7843 i m\'ecnh n\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y may m\'e0 v\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh \u259 n \u273 i\u7875 m t\'e2m ho\u7863 c l\'e0 b\u7919 a khuya kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai m\uc0\u7855 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u b\u7883  kh\u259 n l\u7909 a \u273 en che, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7907 i \u259 n t\u7889 i xong m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7843  c\u7853 u \u273 i, n\'ean c\u7853 u hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  nghe theo l\u7901 i \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng vi\u7879 c g\'ec kh\'e1c \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, y\'ean t\u297 nh n\u7857 m \u273 \'f3, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i m\'e0 c\u361 ng y\'ean t\u297 nh ng\u7891 i \u7903  b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 ang nh\'ecn m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\'ecn m\'ecnh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  l\u7841 i mu\u7889 n \u259 n? C\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7883 n \u273 \u7871 n th\u7901 i gian b\u7919 a t\u7889 i kh\'f4ng? Tr\'ec Di\'ean y\'ean l\u7863 ng ngh\u297  trong b\u7909 ng, l\'fac \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i n\u7891 i l\u7849 u hay m\'f3n c\'e1 n\u432 \u7899 ng y\'eau th\'edch, n\u7871 u \u273 \u7893 i th\'e0nh b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'ec h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7881  nh\'ecn m\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  xong vi\u7879 c s\u7869  b\u7883  v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng kia kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\'e0o t\u7899 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\'fat m\'e1u, th\u7847 m suy ngh\u297  ng\'e0i mu\u7889 n h\'fat th\'ec c\u7913  h\'fat, d\'f9 sao t\'f4i m\u7863 c k\u7879  ng\'e0i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\u7843 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\'e0i, t\'f4i th\u7853 t s\u7921  bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 , t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'fac h\'fat m\'e1u ng\'e0i n\'ean nh\u7865  m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7915 ng c\'f3 \u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c t\'f4i. Tuy r\u7857 ng ch\'ednh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t nguy\u7879 n v\u7885 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7883  l\'e0m t\u7881 nh kia g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \'e1nh m\u7855 t nh\u432  c\'f3 nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\'e0 ng\u7911  say s\u432 a, t\u7921  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh nh\u432  con th\u7887  ng\u7911  c\u7841 nh mi\u7879 ng l\'e3o h\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\u7853 y m\'e0 ng\u7911  r\u7845 t ngon, trong ph\'f2ng lu\'f4n r\u7845 t y\'ean t\u297 nh, gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng r\u7845 t tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u l\'e0 ng\u7911  no r\u7891 i t\u7921  t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i. C\u7853 u th\u7917  gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh \u273 ang n\u7857 m trong ng\u7921 c m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\'e1nh tay ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng kho\'e1t tr\'ean h\'f4ng c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u d\u7921 a v\'e0o b\u7843  vai ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 . Ch\'f3p m\u361 i v\u7845 n v\'edt kh\'ed t\u7913 c quen thu\u7897 c, l\'e0 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  tr\'e1nh m\u7897 t h\'fat, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c n\u7857 m b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c li\u7873 n bu\'f4ng c\u7853 u ra ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  l\'e0 m\u7845 y gi\u7901  r\u7891 i? Sao kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c t\'f4i?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng h\u7887 i, trong gi\u7885 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n mang theo ch\'fat gi\u7885 ng m\u361 i bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  ch\u432 a t\u7881 nh h\u7859 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'e1m r\uc0\u432 \u7905 i. V\u7915 a r\u7891 i t\'f4i c\u361 ng ng\u7911  n\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd." Nh\u432 ng th\u7853 t ra l\'e0 th\u7845 y c\u7853 u ng\u7911  ngon qu\'e1, t\'e2m kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao li\u7873 n m\u7873 m th\'e0nh m\u7897 t m\u7843 nh, kh\'f4ng n\u7905  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c gi\'e0y v\'f2 c\u7853 u, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng n\u7905  \u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c, d\u7913 t kho\'e1t th\u7915 a c\u417  \'f4m c\u7853 u song song n\u7857 m c\'f9ng nhau.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, n\u7897 i t\'e2m c\'f3 ch\'fat kinh d\u7883 , h\'f3a ra qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u361 ng bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  \'e0? C\u361 ng \u273 \'fang, trong phim c\u361 ng n\'f3i b\u7885 n h\u7885  ng\u7911  trong quan t\'e0i, ng\'e0y ng\u7911  \u273 \'eam th\u7913 c. Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ban ng\'e0y kh\'f4ng ng\u7911 , ng\u7911  l\u7841 i c\'f2n d\'f9ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y ch\uc0\u7881  nghe qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'f3i: "Ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 \'e3 t\u7881 nh, ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  \u259 n r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\u7841 i treo l\'ean theo nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u quy\u7871 t t\'e2m, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u qua tr\'e1i: "L\u7847 n n\'e0y n\'ean c\u7855 n b\'ean ph\u7843 i nh\u7881 ?" Hai b\'ean tr\'e1i ph\u7843 i tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7893  v\'e0 g\'e1y \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  c\u7855 n, l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u7855 n b\'ean ph\u7843 i, l\u7847 n sau c\u7855 n b\'ean tr\'e1i, t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng chia \u273 \u7873 u, r\u7845 t c\'f4ng b\u7857 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, th\u7845 y th\u7871  nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u432 \u7901 i qu\u7923  m\u7897 t g\u7889 i l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, n\u7857 m b\'ean c\u7841 nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\'fan xu\u7889 ng, kh\'ed t\u7913 c qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n m\'ecnh, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng. T\'e2m tr\u7841 ng c\u7853 u b\'e2y gi\u7901  nh\u432  khi c\'f2n b\'e9 \u273 i ti\'eam ng\u7915 a, m\u7897 t m\u7863 t ngh\u297  ti\'eam th\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n ti\'eam, m\u7897 t m\u7863 t l\u7841 i ngh\u297  d\'f9 sao s\u7899 m mu\u7897 n g\'ec c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n ph\u7843 i ti\'eam, kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng s\u7899 m ti\'eam cho xong \u273 \u7905  ph\u7843 i lo l\u7855 ng s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, \u7903  b\'ean c\u7893  ph\u7843 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u7845 n xu\u7889 ng m\u7897 t n\u7909  h\'f4n l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh: "... G\u7885 i ng\u432 \u417 i \u259 n c\u417 m, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ta mu\u7889 n \u259 n ng\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \'e1p l\u7921 c tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c n\'f3i xong c\'e2u \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y t\u259 m h\u417 i \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\'e1t sau h\u7855 n tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, d\u7855 t c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i chi\u7871 c b\'e0n s\u7901  th\u7845 y l\'fac m\u7899 i t\u7899 i, d\u7851 n c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f3 hi\uc0\u7875 u, kh\'f4ng r\'f5 v\'ec sao v\u7883  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  n\'e0y th\'e0 t\u7841 o th\'eam phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c cho b\u7843 n th\'e2n nh\u432  th\u7871  ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7875  m\'ecnh th\'e1o kh\u259 n xu\u7889 ng. H\u7855 n c\u7913  kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\'e1ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n v\u7853 y sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f9i c\uc0\u417 m th\u417 m c\u361 ng \u273 ang d\u7909  ho\u7863 c c\u7853 u, l\'fac \u273 ang \u259 n tr\u432 a Grey \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u, l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\'e1ch bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a t\'e1m gi\u7901 , m\'e0 c\u7853 u b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u r\u7891 i l\u7841 i m\u7897 t h\u7841 t c\u417 m c\u361 ng ch\u432 a v\'e0o b\u7909 ng, \u273 ang th\u7901 i k\'ec tu\u7893 i tr\u7867  sung s\u7913 c, \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m kh\'f4ng k\'ecm n\'e9n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'f3i b\u7909 ng. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i \u259 n ki\u7875 u g\'ec, d\'f9 sao c\'e1i g\'ec c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac b\uc0\u7909 ng r\'e9o vang nghe \u273 \u7891  \u259 n m\'f9i th\u417 m l\u7841 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7891 i kh\'f4ng, t\u432  v\u7883  n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\u7877  ch\u7883 u ch\'fat n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i: "C\'f3 b\'f2 b\'edt t\u7871 t, \u273 \'f9i c\u7915 u n\u432 \u7899 ng, c\u361 ng c\'f3 c\'e0 ri t\'f4m, m\'ec h\u7843 i s\u7843 n, \u7915 m, c\'f2n c\'f3 g\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 ng, c\'e1 chi\'ean gi\'f2n v\'e0 salad rau. M\'f3n ch\'ednh l\'e0 khoai t\'e2y n\u432 \u7899 ng v\'e0 b\'e1nh m\'ec b\u417  t\u7887 i, n\u432 \u7899 c canh c\'f3 s\'fap n\u7845 m v\'e0 s\'fap rau c\u7911 , \u273 i\u7875 m t\'e2m c\'f3 b\'e1nh chocolate v\'e0 b\'e1nh tart v\u7883  chanh. Ng\u432 \u417 i mu\u7889 n \u259 n g\'ec tr\u432 \u7899 c?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean qu\'e1 m\uc0\u7913 c kinh d\u7883  n\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u7847 m ng\'e2m m\u7897 t ch\'fat: "Ng\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng quen \u259 n nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y? V\u7853 y ng\u432 \u417 i mu\u7889 n \u259 n g\'ec?" Tuy r\u7857 ng hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  \u273 \u7847 u b\u7871 p \u273 \'e3 v\u7873 , nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n tin t\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m m\u7897 t \'edt \u273 \u7891  \u259 n Trung Qu\u7889 c m\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n, t\'f4i \u259 n g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c." Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7897 i v\'e0ng n\'f3i. Tr\'ean th\u7921 c t\u7871  c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7911 ng \'e1i m\'e0 lo s\u7907 . C\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n cho r\u7857 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng ma \u273 \u7847 u qu\u7927  d\u7919 , kh\'f4ng th\u7875  hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 ang l\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n qu\u7927  d\u7883  g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c hi\u7875 u bi\u7871 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\u7873  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u v\u7851 n qu\'e1 \'edt, h\u417 n n\u7919 a r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i phim \u7843 nh ti\u7875 u thuy\u7871 t l\u7915 a b\u7883 p, l\'fac n\'e0o tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\u7843 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7887 i xem v\'ec sao Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng l\u7841 i l\'e0m v\u7853 y. Ho\u7863 c l\'e0 c\u7853 u n\'ean h\u7865 n v\u7883  b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u th\u7907  s\u259 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 i g\u7863 p nhau m\u7897 t l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
