\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer sau khi nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u tr\u7843  l\u7901 i r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh: "V\u7853 y th\u7917  m\u7895 i lo\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo gi\'e1c quan c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 t\u7887 a nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i b\'ean mi\u7879 ng, c\'f3 m\'f9i d\u7847 u \u259 n v\'e0 m\'f9i gia v\u7883 . C\u7853 u l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng \u259 n v\'e0o.L\'e0 \u273 \'f9i c\u7915 u n\u432 \u7899 ng, th\u7883 t c\u7915 u ngon m\'e0 nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c, n\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7915 a \u273 \u7911 , kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u gia v\u7883 , ch\u7881  r\u7855 c \'edt mu\u7889 i v\'e0 ti\'eau, k\u7871 t h\u7907 p v\u7899 i v\u7883  t\u432 \u417 i ngon nguy\'ean v\u7883  nguy\'ean ch\u7845 t c\u7911 a th\u7883 t, \u273 \'edch th\u7921 c l\'e0 b\u7919 a ti\u7879 c th\u7883 nh so\u7841 n c\u7911 a v\u7883  gi\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi do d\uc0\u7921  nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mu\u7889 n \u259 n mi\u7871 ng th\u7913  hai.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\'e0i c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\'f4i. T\'f4i th\'e1o kh\u259 n xu\u7889 ng t\u7921  \u259 n l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i." C\u7853 u c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7845 t an n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, ch\u7881  tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c d\'f9ng h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7875  hi\u7879 n th\'e1i \u273 \u7897 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y \u273 \'fat t\u7899 i b\'ean mi\u7879 ng l\'e0 m\'ec h\u7843 i s\u7843 n. V\u7883  h\u7843 i s\u7843 n bao ph\u7911  m\'ec \'dd dai m\u7873 m tuy kh\'f4ng kh\'f3 \u259 n, nh\u432 ng so s\'e1nh v\u7899 i th\u7883 t c\u7915 u n\u432 \u7899 ng th\'ec c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi l\uc0\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... T\'f4i c\'f2n mu\u7889 n \u259 n th\u7883 t c\u7915 u kia."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\'ean tai h\u417 i n\'f3ng l\'ean. H\'ecnh nh\u432  m\'ecnh l\u7841 i l\'e0m m\u7845 t m\u7863 t lo\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  \u273 \'edch th\'e2n h\u7847 u h\u7841  c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p \u259 n xong b\u7919 a t\u7889 i c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 ho\'e0n m\u7929 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n \u259 n c\u417 m n\'e0y, sau khi vui s\u432 \u7899 ng \u259 n li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c d\'f9ng g\'ec \u273 \u7875  \u273 \'fat, trong b\u7889 n l\u7847 n cho \u259 n ch\u7881  c\u7847 n c\'f3 ba l\u7847 n d\'f9ng th\'eca, m\u7897 t l\u7847 n c\'f2n l\u7841 i thay b\u7857 ng v\u7853 t g\'ec th\'ec c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ki\u7875 m tra. M\'e0 n\'f3i th\u7853 t b\u7919 a c\u417 m n\'e0y so v\u7899 i c\u417 m m\'ecnh chi\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t x\u7883 n h\u417 n bao nhi\'eau, so v\u7899 i tay ngh\u7873  c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n c\u361 ng m\u7929  v\u7883  h\u417 n bao nhi\'eau. Ng\u432 \u7901 i \u259 n no th\u7887 a m\'e3n r\u7891 i s\u7869  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y vui v\u7867  l\u7841 i h\'e0i l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  n\'f3i mu\u7889 n h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u, ch\u7881  n\'f3i Grey \u273 ang ch\u7901  c\u7853 u \u7903  ngo\'e0i, s\u7869  \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7919 a t\u7889 i v\'e0 gi\u7845 c ng\u7911  ngon l\'fac chi\u7873 u kia l\'e0m Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\'e0nh tr\'ecnh ng\'e0y h\'f4m nay c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 . C\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c y\'eau c\u7847 u c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i sinh ho\u7841 t th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng th\u7845 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\u7855 t c\u7853 u \u273 i t\u7899 i g\u7847 n c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng li\u7873 n bu\'f4ng c\u7853 u ra, \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u t\u7921  m\u7903  c\u7917 a r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7863 t tay l\'ean tay n\u7855 m c\u7917 a, l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y eo m\'ecnh b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7841 nh m\u7869  \'f4m l\u7845 y\'97\'97 c\'f9ng l\'fac \u273 \'f3 r\u259 ng nanh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 nhanh ch\'f3ng c\u7855 m v\'e0o b\'ean ph\u7843 i c\u7893  c\u7853 u. T\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u ph\'e1t sinh tr\u7903  tay kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng l\u7847 n h\'fat m\'e1u n\'e0y l\u7841 i c\u7921 c k\u7923  ng\u7855 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t tay n\u7855 m c\u7917 a, v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\u7855 m ch\u7863 t m\u7855 t, mi\u7879 ng h\u417 i m\u7903 , nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng ngh\u7865 n ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  than nh\u7865 , kho\'e1i c\u7843 m b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u v\u7915 a x\'f4ng l\'ean n\'e3o, r\u259 ng nanh \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i c\u417  th\u7875 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng li\u7871 m mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u, d\'f9ng \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i cu\u7889 n \u273 i huy\u7871 t ch\'e2u th\u7853 t nh\u7887  th\u7845 m ra l\'fac r\u259 ng r\'fat ra: "... Xin l\u7895 i, ta kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  t\u7921  ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng mu\u7889 n h\'fat m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i, nh\u432 ng nh\'e1y m\u7855 t tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y em mu\u7889 n r\u7901 i \u273 i, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o ng\u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'e1t v\u7885 ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7897 c chi\u7871 m em, gi\u7919  em \u7903  b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c h\'f4n nh\u7865  n\u417 i c\u7893  c\u7853 u b\u7883  t\u7853 p k\'edch, ki\'ean nh\u7851 n ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7899 i r\u259 ng m\'f4i m\'ecnh t\u7915  t\u7915  b\'ecnh ph\u7909 c: "... H\'f4m nay \u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe v\uc0\u7853 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, m\u7903  to hai m\u7855 t, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\'f3 ph\u7847 n s\u7907  h\'e3i. Tuy nhi\'ean n\'e9t m\u7863 t c\u7853 u d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7899 p kh\u259 n l\u7909 a \u273 en c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng v\u432 \u417 n tay k\'e9o c\u7917 a cho c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i im \u7855 ng r\u7901 i \u273 i, h\u7859 n l\'e0 tr\u7903  v\u7873  trong ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'e2n c\uc0\u7853 u b\u432 \u7899 c d\u7915 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 i ra kh\u7887 i c\u259 n ph\'f2ng. C\'e1nh c\u7917 a l\'e0m b\u7857 ng g\u7895  n\u7863 ng n\u7873  ph\'eda sau m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a y\'ean l\u7863 ng kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng kh\'e9p l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 a tay th\'e1o kh\u259 n l\u7909 a xu\u7889 ng, d\'f9ng tay \u273 \'e8 l\'ean tr\'e1n che \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n. C\u7843  to\'e0 nh\'e0 \'e1nh s\'e1ng r\u7845 t y\u7871 u, m\u7901  nh\u7841 t m\'e0 u \'e1m, sau khi th\'e1o kh\u259 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 th\'edch \u7913 ng v\u7899 i ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t. Grey qu\u7843  nhi\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  l\u7847 u m\u7897 t ch\u7901  c\u7853 u, chi\u7871 c xe m\'e0u \u273 en kia \u273 ang \u273 \u7895  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 \'e3 g\u7847 n m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  t\u7889 i, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\u7889  Sophus xe c\u7897  \'edt h\u417 n, \u273 \u7841 i b\u7897  ph\u7853 n hai b\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\u7901  m\u7901  c\'f9ng d\'e2n c\u432  y\'ean t\u297 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe d\uc0\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7853 u n\'f3i c\'e1m \u417 n v\u7899 i Grey xong xu\u7889 ng xe, chi\u7871 c \'e1o kho\'e1c ngo\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en v\u7851 n c\u7847 m trong tay nh\u432  c\u361 . L\'fac c\u7853 u \u273 i g\u7863 p v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean c\u7847 m xu\u7889 ng xe, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean \u273 em n\'f3 tr\u7843  l\u7841 i cho ch\u7911  nh\'e2n c\u7911 a n\'f3, m\'e0 Grey t\u7915  ch\u7889 i gi\'fap c\u7853 u tr\u7843  h\u7897 , cho n\'ean c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  c\u7847 m b\u7897  y ph\u7909 c n\'e0y v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c xe c\u7913 u th\u432 \u417 ng m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng \u273 ang \u273 \u7895 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c li\u7871 c chi\u7871 c xe kia th\'eam m\u7845 y l\u7847 n, suy \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec. L\'e0 sinh vi\'ean b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng hay \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7917 a k\'ednh ngo\'e0i k\'ed t\'fac c\u226 \u768 n qu\'e9t th\u7867  m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7903 , ngay l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a t\'ecm th\u7867  sinh vi\'ean, m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4 l\u7899 n v\u7897 i v\'e3 t\u7915  trong lao ra, c\u7853 u v\u7897 i v\'e0ng lui qua m\u7897 t b\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kia l\'e0 m\uc0\u7897 t nh\'f3m ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7863 c \'e1o blouse tr\u7855 ng, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 ang n\'e2ng m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  to\'e0n th\'e2n b\u7883  tr\'f3i tr\'ean c\'e1ng c\u7913 u th\u432 \u417 ng nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng gi\'e3y d\u7909 a, kh\'ed l\u7921 c c\'f4 ta r\u7845 t l\u7899 n, h\'e0nh vi ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng b\u7883  kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t tr\'ed, v\u7863 n v\u7865 o c\u7893 , mi\u7879 ng h\'e1 l\u7899 n, \'fd \u273 \u7891  c\u7855 n nh\'e2n vi\'ean y t\u7871  c\'e1ch m\'ecnh g\u7847 n nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f3c c\'f4 ta ho\'e0n to\'e0n r\uc0\u7889 i tung, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t t\'e1i nh\u7907 t, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng d\u7919  t\u7907 n, l\u7841 i tho\'e1ng l\u7897  ra v\'e0i ph\u7847 n qu\u7927  d\u7883 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7845 t n\u7917 a ph\'fat m\u7899 i ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t nh\u7853 n ra, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  ch\'ednh l\'e0 Emily!\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i theo ph\'eda sau l\'e0 c\'f4 Julia tr\u7921 c ban h\'f4m nay v\'e0 Caroline, b\u7841 n c\u7911 a Emily, c\'f4 Julia theo sau c\'f9ng l\'ean xe c\u7913 u th\u432 \u417 ng, Caroline th\'ec b\u7883  khuy\'ean gi\u7919  l\u7841 i. R\u7845 t nhanh xe c\u7913 u th\u432 \u417 ng mang theo t\u7845 t c\u7843  ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng h\u7895 n t\u7841 p \u7847 m \u297  \u273 i xa, c\u7917 a t\'fac x\'e1 m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c y\'ean t\u297 nh, ti\u7871 ng n\u7913 c n\u7903  v\'e0 l\u7849 m b\u7849 m c\u7911 a Caroline li\u7873 n tr\u7903  n\'ean c\u7921 c k\'ec r\'f5 r\'e0ng.\cb1 \
