\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7883 nh g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, v\u7843  l\u7841 i tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a Emily v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c li\'ean quan.\cb1 \
