\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\u7875  cho h\u7855 n cu\u7897 c g\u7863 p bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a \u7903  ch\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, c\u361 ng n\'f3i ra nghi ng\u7901  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh: "Em kh\'f4ng r\'f5 t\u7841 i sao h\u7855 n ph\u7843 i gi\u7919  em l\u7841 i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i c\'f9ng \u259 n t\u7889 i. \u272 \u7871 n l\'fac cu\u7889 i h\u7855 n ch\u7881  h\'fat \'edt m\'e1u c\u7911 a em, h\u417 n n\u7919 a h\'ecnh nh\u432  h\u7855 n v\u7889 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh h\'fat m\'e1u, n\'ean h\u7855 n gi\u7919  em l\u7841 i ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 \'fd ngh\u297 a g\'ec c\u7843 ."\cb1 \
