\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 gi\u7843 i th\'edch ki\u7875 u qu\u7927  g\'ec \u273 \'e2y, c\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 g\u7885 i l\'e0 "C\u7843 m gi\'e1c t\u7921  tay \u273 \'fat c\u7853 u \u259 n" ... Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7847 m m\u7855 ng m\u7897 t c\'e2u trong b\u7909 ng, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1p \'e1n g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng tin t\u7915  trong mi\u7879 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f2n c\'f3, h\'f4m nay Emily \uc0\u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n. C\'f4 \u7845 y nh\u432  b\u7883  m\u7845 t tr\'ed, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t t\'e1i nh\u7907 t, li\'ean t\u7909 c mu\u7889 n c\u7855 n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh, tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn kh\'ed l\u7921 c c\u361 ng m\u7841 nh b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, anh c\'f3 bi\u7871 t l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ean kia tr\uc0\u7847 m ng\'e2m m\u7897 t l\'e1t, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "V\u7853 y c\'f4 \u7845 y h\u7859 n l\'e0 b\u7883  nhi\u7877 m r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7883  nhi\u7877 m?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, x\'e1c th\u7921 c m\'e0 n\'f3i, tuy r\u7857 ng r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u361 ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 bi\u7871 n \u273 \u7893 i t\u7915  nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i m\'e0 th\'e0nh, nh\u432 ng th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7885 n h\u7885  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  k\'e9o d\'e0i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a h\u7885 , b\u7885 n h\u7885  ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'f4 tri d\u7921 a v\'e0o m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7875  duy tr\'ec t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u417  b\u7843 n. Cho n\'ean c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  x\'e1c s\u7889 ng, b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7855 n c\u361 ng c\'f3 nguy c\u417  b\u7883  nhi\u7877 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\'e2n lo\uc0\u7841 i b\u7883  nhi\u7877 m s\u7869  c\'f3 ba k\u7871 t qu\u7843 : M\u7897 t l\'e0 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u th\'f4ng qua c\'e1ch n\'e0y chuy\u7875 n h\'f3a th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c s\u7869  t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i y\u7871 u, kh\'f4ng m\u7841 nh nh\u432  \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7897 c th\'f4ng qua nghi th\u7913 c *S\u417  \u7910 ng ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n ch\'ednh th\u7913 c m\'e0 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, s\u7869  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p th\u7845 p nh\u7845 t; th\u7913  hai l\'e0 tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p t\u7917  vong v\'ec b\u7883  nhi\u7877 m; th\u7913  ba l\'e0 s\u7869  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\'e1i v\u7853 t m\u7845 t tr\'ed ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n t\u7845 n c\'f4ng k\u7867  kh\'e1c, h\u417 n n\u7919 a trong qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh n\'e0y sinh m\u7841 ng s\u7869  d\u7847 n d\u7847 n hao m\'f2n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng tr\u7903  th\'e0nh k\u7867  v\'f4 tri nh\u432  x\'e1c s\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'fd tr\'ed kh\'f4ng c\'f3 sinh m\u7841 ng, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  b\u7883  th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ho\u7863 c l\'e0 khu ma s\u432  x\u7917  l\'fd. Nh\u432  l\u7901 i c\u7853 u k\u7875  th\'ec c\'f4 ta h\u7859 n l\'e0 g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p th\u7913  ba r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
