\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7899  c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7889 i Alex \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm m\'ecnh r\u7911  m\'ecnh \u273 i ch\u417 i nh\u432 ng m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng \u273 i, sau \u273 \'f3 Emily theo \u273 \'e1m b\u7885 n h\u7885  r\u7901 i \u273 i, h\'f4m sau l\'fac c\u7853 u d\u7853 y nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7893  tay Emily b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7843 y r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u m\'e1u. \u272 \'eam h\'f4m \u273 \'f3, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 s\u7899 m h\u417 n tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 Emily c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i ch\u7907 t ph\'e1t gi\'e1c m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t \'97\'97 n\u7871 u nh\u432  Emily l\'e0 v\'ec b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7855 n m\u7899 i b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng, v\u7853 y t\u7841 i sao v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a c\'f4 l\u7841 i ch\u7843 y nhi\u7873 u m\'e1u nh\u432  th\u7871 ? C\u259 n c\u7913  theo kinh nghi\u7879 m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer m\u7895 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7873 u li\u7871 m s\u7841 ch m\'e1u gi\u7885 t th\u7845 m ra, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u259 n b\u7843 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u mang v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873 . D\'f9 cho nh\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia c\u7845 p b\u7853 c kh\'f4ng cao b\u7857 ng Emmer, ch\u7843 y nhi\u7873 u m\'e1u nh\u432  th\u7871  th\'ec c\u361 ng th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng n\'f3i n\u7893 i...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i ngh\u297  lui \u273 \'e3 \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng gi\u7863 t \u273 \u7891 , trong n\'e0y t\'edn hi\u7879 u kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t l\u7855 m, c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i thu qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u361 ng b\u7845 t ti\u7879 n. C\u7853 u \u273 ang mu\u7889 n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng h\u7865 n th\u7901 i gian g\u7863 p Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, sau \u273 \'f3 t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t t\u7855 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en hi\u7879 n l\'ean t\u7915  ph\'eda b\'ean ph\u7843 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\u7909 i d\u7909 i m\u7855 t, t\u432 \u7903 ng l\'e0 m\'ecnh m\u7845 t m\'e1u qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u n\'ean hoa m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u v\u7853 y th\'ec l\u7847 n sau ph\u7843 i \u273 i t\'ecm Emmer khi\u7871 u n\u7841 i, n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, n\u7871 u mu\u7889 n duy tr\'ec ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c th\'ec h\u7855 n ph\u7843 i h\'fat \'edt m\'e1u \u273 i ch\'fat, gi\u7843 m s\u7889  l\u432 \u7907 ng gi\u7843 m s\u7889  l\u7847 n m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i m\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en kh\'f4ng r\'f5 ch\u7907 t hi\u7879 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i m\'ecnh m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7897 p" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c khom l\u432 ng nh\u7863 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c c\u7853 u c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng \u273 \'e8n ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean t\u7855 t, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a tr\u432 \u7899 c sau \u273 \u7873 u "C\u7841 ch" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng kh\'e9p l\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng gian kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\'e2m v\'e0o trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i b\u7883  phong b\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c th\u7859 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 b\u7889 n ph\'eda.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'f3ng \uc0\u273 en v\u7915 a r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 l\u7895 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 ang ti\u7873 m ph\u7909 c xung quanh c\u7853 u, ch\u7901  th\u7901 i m\'e0 \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7855 t c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o th\'edch \u7913 ng v\u7899 i khung c\u7843 nh t\u7889 i \u273 en, nh\u432 ng trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i l\u7841 i c\'f3 m\u7845 y \u273 i\u7875 m s\'e1ng \u273 \u7887  nh\u432  m\'e1u \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t d\u7877  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ch\'fa \'fd\'97\'97 ch\'fang v\u7851 n lu\'f4n theo d\'f5i c\u7853 u, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'e0 hai m\u7855 t th\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia chi\u7871 m c\u7913  v\u7883  tr\'ed hai b\'ean c\u7917 a, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7913  \u273 ang quanh qu\u7849 n g\u7847 n m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 trong gi\'e2y l\'e1t n\'e0y, ti\uc0\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n, ti\u7871 ng sinh vi\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i trong h\'e0nh lang \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, t\u7921 a nh\u432  ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u7853 u b\u7883  ng\u259 n c\'e1ch trong c\u259 n ph\'f2ng gi\u7863 t \u273 \u7891  nh\u7887  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\'e0m b\uc0\u7915 a, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  v\'e2y quanh m\'ecnh kia l\'e0 g\'ec, ch\u7881  c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\u7863 ng l\u7869  t\'ednh kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch gi\u7919 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a, nh\u7899  l\u7841 i c\'e1ch b\'e0i tr\'ed v\'e0 ch\u432 \u7899 ng ng\u7841 i v\u7853 t \u7903  gi\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7891 i ch\u7901  ch\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \'edt nh\u7845 t ph\u7843 i ch\u7841 y ra kh\u7887 i c\u259 n ph\'f2ng n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nguy c\uc0\u417  kh\'f4ng r\'f5 \u273 \'e3 k\'edch th\'edch t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  t\u432  duy t\u259 ng cao, trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u h\'ecnh th\'e0nh m\u7897 t k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch r\'f5 r\'e0ng, l\u7841 i nhanh ch\'f3ng di\u7877 n luy\u7879 n h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng k\u7871  ti\u7871 p hai l\u7847 n, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c n\'e9m ch\u7891 ng qu\u7847 n \'e1o trong tay m\'ecnh qua b\'ean ph\u7843 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 qu\u7847 n \'e1o m\u7887 ng m\u7863 c th\u7901 i gian tr\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng n\u7863 ng m\u7845 y, c\u361 ng r\u7845 t d\u7877  h\'fat l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f9ng l\'fac \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7917 a tr\'e1i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  trong d\u7921  t\'ednh thu\u7853 n tay k\'e9o ph\u7847 n \u7889 ng h\'fat b\u7909 i b\u7857 ng nh\u7921 a d\u7867 o tho\'e1ng c\u7843 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i. H\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng n\'e0y cho c\u7853 u th\u7901 i gian tranh th\u7911  \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a ra. V\'f4 c\'f9ng may m\u7855 n l\'e0, c\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 kh\'f3a c\u7911 a c\u7917 a b\'ean tr\'e1i \u273 \'e3 h\u7887 ng, m\u7845 y ng\'e0y nay v\u7851 n lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng kh\'f3a, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng ch\'fat tr\u7903  ng\u7841 i m\'e0 ph\'e1 c\u7917 a tho\'e1t ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ean ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng gi\uc0\u7863 t v\u7851 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n y\'ean t\u297 nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng tim \u273 \u7853 p c\'f9ng ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n m\'ecnh m\u7897 t m\'ecnh ch\u7841 y tr\'ean m\u7863 t th\u7843 m, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng c\'e1c b\u7841 n h\u7885 c t\'e1n g\u7851 u n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t trong ph\'f2ng hay ti\u7871 ng c\'e1c ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh tr\'ean m\u7841 ng hay tr\'ean TV truy\u7873 n ra \'97\'97 t\'f2a nh\'e0 n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 t\u7915  l\'e2u l\u7855 m r\u7891 i, hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  c\'e1ch \'e2m c\u7911 a c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i ngang qua l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng b\'ean trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e8n h\'e0nh lang m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng d\u432 \u7899 i b\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed y\'ean t\u297 nh qu\u7927  d\u7883  n\'e0y tr\u7903  n\'ean \'e2m u l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t b\'ean ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 n, m\u7897 t b\'ean li\'ean t\u7909 c l\u7899 n ti\u7871 ng h\'f4 "Help", th\u7871  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7845 t k\u7923  ai xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi ch\uc0\u7841 y t\u7847 m m\u432 \u7901 i m\'e9t, trong l\'fac s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'f3 linh c\u7843 m, quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i li\u7871 c m\u7855 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c nh\'ecn th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \u273 ang v\'e2y b\u7855 t c\u7853 u kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fang c\'f3 l\uc0\u7899 p l\'f4ng d\'e0y s\u7853 m m\'e0u, t\u7913  chi m\u7841 nh m\u7869 , m\'f3ng vu\u7889 t s\u7855 c nh\u7885 n, r\u259 ng nanh \'e1nh h\'e0n quang, c\'f9ng v\u7899 i con m\u7855 t \u273 \u7887  nh\u432  m\'e1u \u273 \u7909 c ng\u7847 u hung t\'e0n \'97\'97 \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 s\'f3i, m\u7895 i con \u273 \u7873 u v\'f4 c\'f9ng c\u432 \u7901 ng h\'e3n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\'fat nghi ng\u7901  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  th\u7845 y m\'e1u d\u432 \u7899 i r\u259 ng nanh m\'f3ng vu\u7889 t c\u7911 a ch\'fang, ch\'fang r\u7845 t gi\u7887 i vi\u7879 c c\u7855 n \u273 \u7913 t y\u7871 t h\u7847 u con m\u7891 i, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7855 n x\'e9 r\'e1ch b\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f9ng l\'e0 d\'e3 th\'fa, nh\uc0\u7919 ng con s\'f3i n\'e0y so v\u7899 i s\'f3i c\u7853 u th\u7845 y trong phim t\'e0i li\u7879 u hay v\u432 \u7901 n th\'fa l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta khi\u7871 p s\u7907  h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 l\'fac n\'e0y con s\'f3i g\uc0\u7847 n c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 ang nh\u7843 y l\'ean cao, ch\'e2n tr\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3 \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p v\u7899 i t\u7899 i l\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\'fat nghi ng\u7901  m\u7897 t gi\'e2y sau m\'ecnh s\u7869  b\u7883  n\'f3 lao v\'e0o. C\u7853 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t con ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u259 ng l\u7921 c b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o tr\u7889 n tho\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng con th\'fa n\'e0y v\u7891  gi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y, trong h\'e0nh lang tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng vang l\'ean ti\u7871 ng th\u7911 y tinh v\u7905 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Con s\'f3i kia trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t ng\u7915 ng \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7843 m \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3, c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c n\u7857 m r\u7841 p xu\u7889 ng sau l\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, b\'e0y ra t\u432  th\u7871  ph\'f2ng ng\u7921 , m\u7845 y con s\'f3i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7857 ng sau c\u361 ng r\'ean l\'ean t\u7915  t\u7915  l\'f9i v\u7873  ph\'eda sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda \'e2m thanh truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 \'eam \u273 \'e3 khuya, th\u7911 y tinh tr\'ean c\u7917 a s\u7893  r\u417 i h\u432 \u7899 ng v\'e0o trong v\u259 ng \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7845 t, gi\'f3 \u273 \'eam t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i th\u7893 i v\'e0o, mang theo m\'e1t m\u7867  ng\'e0y thu. C\u7843 nh \u273 \'eam tr\u7847 m l\u7855 ng, m\'e0n \u273 \'eam v\'f4 t\u7853 n tr\'ean tr\u7901 i cao, d\u432 \u7899 i t\u7847 ng m\'e2y m\u7901  l\u7919 ng l\u7901  tr\'f4i kh\u7855 p n\u417 i c\'f3 th\u7875  tho\'e1ng tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y n\u7917 a v\u7847 ng tr\u259 ng tr\'f2n, \'e2m l\u7883 ch h\'f4m nay m\'f9ng b\u7843 y, tr\u259 ng th\u432 \u7907 ng huy\u7873 n, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng \'e1nh tr\u259 ng \u273 \u7887  nh\u432  m\'e1u.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (th\uc0\u432 \u7907 ng huy\u7873 n: m\'f9ng 7,8 \'e2m l\u7883 ch)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tho\'e1ng nh\uc0\u432  \u272 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c tr\u7847 n gian.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y l\'e0 ai ph\'e1 c\u7917 a s\u7893 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Con s\'f3i \uc0\u273 en \u7903  g\u7847 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t h\'ecnh th\u7875  c\u7921 c l\u7899 n, d\'e0i ch\u7915 ng hai m\'e9t, n\u7857 m r\u7841 p xu\u7889 ng c\u361 ng cao \u273 \u7871 n ng\u7921 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean, n\'f3 b\u7845 t an ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7845 c ch\'e2n tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'ean, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t k\'edch l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  d\u7889 c s\u7913 c li\u7873 u m\u7897 t l\u7847 n ph\'f3ng v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7845 t ng\u7901  kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng, ch\u7881  k\u7883 p lui v\u7873  sau m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, m\u7855 t th\u7845 y r\u259 ng s\'f3i s\u7855 c nh\u7885 n c\'e1ch b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\'f2n kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 m\u7897 t tay. \u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7845 y hoa m\u7855 t, con s\'f3i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t \u273 \'e3 ng\u7917 a ra sau bay ra ngo\'e0i, nh\'ecn k\u7929  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y d\u432 \u7899 i b\u7909 ng n\'f3 c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng s\'e2u d\'e0i, m\'e1u nhanh ch\'f3ng ch\u7843 y ra, th\u7845 m tr\'ean l\u7899 p l\'f4ng \u273 en kh\'f4ng r\'f5, m\'e1u v\u259 ng tung t\'f3e, c\'f2n c\'f3 l\u432 \u7907 ng l\u7899 n m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i m\'e0u \u273 en ch\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng m\u7863 t th\u7843 m h\'e0nh lang m\'e0u lam.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3 nghi\'eang ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7887  m\'e1u l\u7841 i v\u7851 n g\u7855 t gao d\'e1n v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, n\'f3i \u273 \'fang h\u417 n l\'e0 d\'e1n v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Nh\u7919 ng con s\'f3i kh\'e1c kh\u7869  k\'eau x\'fam xung quanh n\'f3, c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng m\'e0 nh\'ecn b\'ean n\'e0y, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m v\u432 \u7907 t gi\u7899 i h\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7899 i ph\'e2n l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd nh\'ecn \'e2n nh\'e2n c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sophus th\'e1ng t\uc0\u432  kh\'ed tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 chuy\u7875 n l\u7841 nh, trong \u273 \'eam nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  th\u7845 p nh\u7845 t ch\u7881  b\u7843 y t\'e1m \u273 \u7897 . Ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i cao g\u7847 y r\u7855 n r\u7887 i, m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o cho\'e0ng d\'e0i, t\'f3c \u273 en h\u417 i d\'e0i qu\'e1 vai, r\u7911  sau g\'e1y. Tay h\u7855 n th\u7843  hai b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 tay tr\'e1i h\u7855 n, thon d\'e0i tr\u7855 ng nh\u7907 t, nh\'ecn qua l\u7841 i v\'f4 c\'f9ng h\u7919 u l\u7921 c, ng\'f3n \'e1p \'fat tay tr\'e1i \u273 eo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n m\'e0u b\u7841 c d\'e0y, tr\'ean m\u7863 t nh\u7851 n kh\u7855 c hoa v\u259 n n\u7893 i g\u7891  gh\u7873 , m\u7897 t gi\u7885 t m\'e1u \u273 en \u273 ang nh\u7887  xu\u7889 ng t\u7915  ph\u7847 n hoa v\u259 n l\'f5m xu\u7889 ng, nh\u7887  tr\'ean m\u7863 t th\u7843 m m\'e0u lam.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a r\u7891 i h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 d\'f9ng chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n n\'e0y l\'e0m con s\'f3i tr\u7885 ng th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y nam nh\'e2n \uc0\u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean kho\u7843 ng hai b\u432 \u7899 c, y\'ean l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn nh\u7919 ng con s\'f3i kia, t\u7915  g\'f3c \u273 \u7897  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n. H\u7855 n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u273 \u7897 ng, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c uy \'e1p truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n t\u7915  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Lo\uc0\u7841 i \'e1p l\u7921 c v\'e0 kh\'ed t\u7913 c n\'e0y ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i uy hi\u7871 p \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng con s\'f3i kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fang th\uc0\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng k\'eau \u432  \u7917 , nh\u432  \u273 ang b\'e0n b\u7841 c g\'ec \u273 \'f3, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c trong ch\u7899 p m\u7855 t to\'e0n b\u7897  bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, bao g\u7891 m c\u7843  con s\'f3i b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng. M\'e0 nam nh\'e2n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd ng\u259 n c\u7843 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y kinh nghi b\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh v\u7899 i m\u7897 t m\'e0n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda nam nh\'e2n. L\'fac n\'e0y nam nh\'e2n c\u361 ng quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i li\u7871 c nhau m\u7897 t c\'e1i, nam nh\'e2n \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, h\u417 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "Ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f3 bi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u417 i r\u7845 t d\u7877  h\u7845 p d\u7851 n nh\u7919 ng sinh v\u7853 t h\u7855 c \'e1m n\'e0y kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u \'e1p s\'e1t v\'e0o b\'ean tai Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\'edt h\'e0: "Trong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t d\'f2ng kh\'ed t\u7913 c h\u7855 c \'e1m r\u7845 t thu\u7847 n khi\u7871 t, v\u7915 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 kh\'ed t\u7913 c g\u7847 n nh\u432  y h\u7879 t v\u7899 i kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u7903  trong t\u259 m t\u7889 i ch\u7881  l\u7889 i d\u7851 n d\u7855 t h\u7855 n t\u7899 i g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 m\uc0\u7897 t khi t\u7899 i g\u7847 n, c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o bu\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, \u7845 p \'fang n\'f3i: "V\u7915 a r\u7891 i... ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\u7917 a s\u7893  b\u7883  ph\'e1 tan v\'e0 \'e1nh tr\u259 ng \u273 \u7887  nh\u432  m\'e1u b\'ean ngo\'e0i, nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nam nh\'e2n y\'ean l\u7863 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'f3i: "Ch\u7881  l\'e0 tr\'f2 v\u7863 t c\u7911 a m\u7845 y con th\'fa l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng giai \u273 o\u7841 n c\u7911 a tr\u259 ng th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f9ng theo l\uc0\u7901 i h\u7855 n, c\u7917 a s\u7893  b\u7883  v\u7905  \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c nguy\'ean v\u7865 n nh\u432  k\u7923  t\'edch, ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  tr\u7901 i quang m\'e2y t\u7841 nh, \'e1nh s\'e1ng trong tr\u7867 o y\'ean b\'ecnh. Tr\u7901 i cao m\'e2y nh\u7841 t, tr\u259 ng thanh gi\'f3 m\'e1t, ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam thu \u273 \u7865 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong k\'ed t\'fac c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng \u7891 n \'e0o nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c, ti\u7871 ng nh\u7841 c v\'e0 ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i trong ph\'f2ng sinh ho\u7841 t t\u7847 ng tr\'ean \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe r\'f5 r\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 m ch\'ed ngay c\u7843  v\u7871 t m\'e1u tr\'ean m\u7863 t th\u7843 m m\'e1u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7871 t th\u7843 y nh\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  chuy\u7879 n v\u7915 a r\u7891 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 c\u7853 u t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng ra, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh n\'e0y th\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f2n b\u7857 ng ch\u7913 ng n\'e0o kh\'e1c c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7913 ng minh.\cb1 \
