\cb3 "\uc0\u272 inh" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\u7917 a thang m\'e1y m\u7903 , c\'f3 b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\'f9ng t\u7847 ng \u273 i ra t\u7915  trong thang m\'e1y, ch\'e0o Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u361 ng g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\'e0o nam nh\'e2n b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, c\u432 \u7901 i h\u7887 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i: "\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 b\u7841 n c\u7853 u \'e0? \u272 \u7865 p trai qu\'e1 nha."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7863 t c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u."L\'e0 b\u7841 n trai c\u7853 u sao? Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p qua." Ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7887 i, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7913 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i nam nh\'e2n c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, n\u7917 a th\u7853 t n\u7917 a gi\u7843  tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "Sau n\'e0y t\'f4i s\u7869  \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm c\u7853 u \u7845 y nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i r\u7891 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i l\u7841 i quay sang l\u7847 n n\u7919 a nh\'ecn nam nh\'e2n t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\'ecnh t\u297 nh: "Anh r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 ai? T\u7841 i sao l\u7841 i xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y? V\u7915 a r\u7891 i nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia l\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7887 i nhi\u7873 u qu\'e1." Nam nh\'e2n d\u7921 ng th\u7859 ng ng\'f3n tr\u7887  ph\u7843 i kh\u7869  \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean m\'f4i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ng\u259 n c\u7853 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i, "Ch\'fang ta gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t t\u7915 ng c\'e2u m\u7897 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p kh\'f4ng \'edt, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7853 u c\u7853 u th\u7845 y ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\'e0i sinh v\u7853 t h\u7855 c \'e1m kh\'e1c trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i xu\uc0\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 v\'ec nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ch\u7895  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n n\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i v\'f4 h\u7841 i: "T\'f4i l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. A Di\'ean, t\'f4i cho l\'e0 ch\'fang ta \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t r\'f5 v\u7873  nhau r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi du\u7895 i tay tr\'e1i, trong l\'fac gi\'fap Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7917 a l\u7841 i c\u7893  \'e1o x\u7897 c x\u7879 ch l\u7841 i t\u7921  \'fd c\'e0i th\'eam hai n\'fat \'e1o s\u417  mi cho c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7913 c th\'ec m\u432 \u7907 n c\u417  h\u7897 i n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c th\u7845 y r\'f5 hoa v\u259 n tr\'ean chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n m\'e0u b\u7841 c kia \'97\'97 \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t b\u7909 i gai sinh tr\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u417 i t\u7889 t, ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a b\u7909 i gai l\'e0 m\u7897 t b\'f4ng h\u7891 ng c\'f3 v\u7867  y\u7871 u \u7899 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\u7845 n quanh, c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'e0 do t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a k\u7871 t c\u7845 u, d\u432 \u7899 i h\'ecnh d\'e1ng c\'f3 v\u7867  h\u417 i k\u7923  d\u7883  \u273 \u7897 c \'e1c, hoa h\u7891 ng ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i th\u7875  hi\u7879 n ra v\u7867  \u273 \u7865 p v\'f4 l\u7921 c l\u7841 i b\u7873 n b\u7881 , t\u7921 a nh\u432  c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng v\'f4 t\u7853 n v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng t\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh k\uc0\u234 \u769 t h\'f4n r\u244 \u768 i \'e0?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng ng\u7901 , c\u7853 u v\u7853 y m\'e0 v\'f4 th\u7913 c h\u7887 i ra v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  n\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  c\'e2u h\u7887 i v\u7873  cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng ng\'e0y s\u7869  gi\'fap k\'e9o g\u7847 n kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch h\u417 n, l\'e0m b\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed tr\u7903  n\'ean tho\u7843 i m\'e1i h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 kh\'f4ng." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nhu h\'f2a c\u432 \u7901 i, "T\'f4i c\'f2n tr\u7867  th\u7871  n\'e0y m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n xoay chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n tr\'ean tay tr\'e1i: "C\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7853 t n\'e0y sao? \u272 \'e2y ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\'f3n trang s\u7913 c nh\u7887  th\'f4i, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t huy v\'e0i t\'e1c d\u7909 ng kh\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac c\uc0\u7847 n thi\u7871 t c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m v\u361  kh\'ed. Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7847 m b\u7893  sung thay h\u7855 n, th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 m\u7897 t m\'f3n trang s\u7913 c th\u7921 c d\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a s\u7893  h\'e0nh lang, \u273 \u7841 i \u273 a s\u7889  b\u7841 n h\u7885 c sau khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7873 u ch\'e0o h\u7887 i l\u7841 i t\'f2 m\'f2 nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'eam m\u7845 y l\u7847 n, th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t n\u417 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n t\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi x\'e1c nh\uc0\u7853 n th\'e2n ph\u7853 n c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng h\u417 n ph\'e2n n\u7917 a, b\u7845 t an khi l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u g\u7863 p b\u7841 n tr\'ean m\u7841 ng c\u361 ng d\u7847 n bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t. C\u7853 u v\u7851 y tay v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "V\'e2ng, \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng em \u273 i, nh\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  ch\'fang ta ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng gi\u7863 t \u273 \u7891  l\u7845 y qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\u7899 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\u7873  \u273 \'e3."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n r\u417 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u361 ng r\u417 i c\u7841 nh m\'e1y gi\u7863 t, h\u7859 n l\'e0 b\u7883  c\u7853 u n\'e9m qua \u273 \'f3. Xem ra kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai v\'e0o \u273 \'e2y, m\'e0 nh\u7919 ng t\'e0n t\'edch n\'e0y ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7913 ng minh t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n v\u7915 a r\u7891 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  x\u7843 y ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i t\u7915  ph\'f2ng gi\u7863 t qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 i ra, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \'f4m ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 i theo sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Trong tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c s\u417 mi, c\u7853 u h\u417 i ng\u7841 i, \u273 \u7883 nh nh\u7853 n l\u7841 i qu\u7847 n \'e1o t\u7915  trong tay ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean ch\'ednh th\u7913 c g\u7863 p m\u7863 t, l\u7841 i b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\uc0\u7879 c g\'ec, t\'f4i c\u7847 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, ch\'fang ta mau v\u7873  ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\u7897 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t sau \u273 i t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng 407, l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7845 y th\u7867  ph\'f2ng t\u7915  trong t\'fai qu\u7847 n ra \u273 ang chu\u7849 n b\u7883  m\u7903  c\u7917 a th\'ec m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u t\u7915  ph\'f2ng Alex c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i n\'f3i \u273 i ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7891 ng lo\u7841 t im b\u7863 t d\u7915 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a, c\'f3 ch\'fat kinh nghi b\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \'f4m m\u7897 t \u273 \u7889 ng qu\u7847 n \'e1o ch\u7891 ng ch\u7845 t, nh\'ecn c\'f3 v\u7867  nh\u432  \u273 ang \u7903  nh\'e0 h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n c\u7921 c k\u7923  \u273 \u7843 m \u273 ang.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng b\u7885 n h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t r\u7845 t r\'f5 kh\'ed t\u7913 c kh\'f4ng h\u7873  che gi\u7845 u tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kia thu\u7897 c v\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\u7841 nh c\u7845 p cao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean mi\uc0\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 , sau \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n d\'f9ng t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  nhanh nh\u7845 t qu\u7865 t th\u7867  m\u7903  c\u7917 a k\'e9o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i v\'e0o, l\u7841 i kh\'f3a c\u7917 a th\u7853 t k\u7929 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 qu\'ean b\u7857 ng v\u7883  h\u7919 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'e0 m\u7897 t th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  s\u7913 t s\u7865 o, tuy r\u7857 ng tr\'ean danh ngh\u297 a ngh\u7873  nghi\u7879 p v\u7899 i t\u432  c\'e1ch th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  chi\u7871 m \u432 u th\u7871 , nh\u432 ng m\'e0 \u273 \'e1m Alex c\'f2n c\'f3 s\'e1u b\u7843 y ng\u432 \u7901 i. B\u7885 n h\u7885  d\u7915 ng h\u7859 n \u7903  \u273 \'f3 \'e2m th\u7847 m \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, r\'f5 r\'e0ng cho th\u7845 y \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'f3 b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, n\u7871 u nh\u432  b\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0 m\u7897 t th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  r\u7891 i l\u7841 i n\u7893 i l\'ean tranh ch\u7845 p v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, r\'f5 r\'e0ng v\u7883  b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u h\u7885 c ngh\u7879  kh\'f4ng tinh l\u7841 i \u273 \u417 n th\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7897 c m\'e3 th\u7871  \u273 \u417 n l\u7921 c b\u7841 c n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh s\u7869  kh\'f4ng chi\u7871 m \u432 u th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c khi b\u7885 n h\u7855 n ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra th\'e2n ph\u7853 n th\u7853 t c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'ec ph\u7843 i nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 \u432 a h\u7855 n v\'e0o ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh b\u7843 o v\u7879  m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f2n lo l\u7855 ng ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i: "Sao th\u7871 ? C\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 l\u7845 y t\u7915 ng m\'f3n \u273 \u7891  t\u7915  trong tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi treo v\'e0o trong t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 ph\u7889 i h\u7907 p nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\'f4 s\u7889  l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u v\u7915 a treo qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\u7915 a n\'f3i: "V\u7915 a r\u7891 i nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia ch\'ednh l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \'e3 l\u7915 a em \u273 \u7871 n b\u7919 a ti\u7879 c m\'e0 em t\u7915 ng k\u7875  v\u7899 i anh. B\'e2y gi\u7901  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m h\u7919 u d\u361 ng v\'f4 m\u432 u, ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n anh s\u7869  \u273 \'e1nh kh\'f4ng l\u7841 i b\u7885 n h\u7855 n \u273 \'f4ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, cho n\'ean ph\u7843 i nh\'e2n l\'fac bo\u803 n h\u259 \u769 n ch\u432 a ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra anh l\'e0 th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  ch\'fang ta ph\u7843 i nhanh ch\'f3ng v\'e0o nh\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng. H\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  m\'ecnh \u7903  trong m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i l\'e0 h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7907 ng b\u7845 t t\'e0i v\'f4 d\u7909 ng nh\u432  th\u7871 , nh\u7883 n l\u7901 i v\u7889 n \u273 ang \u273 \u7883 nh n\'f3i xu\u7889 ng, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng c\'e3i: "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 y\u7871 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7845 y t\'f4i \u273 u\u7893 i \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i kia \u273 i kh\'f4ng? R\u7845 t l\u7907 i h\u7841 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7915 ng tay nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "N\'ean l\'e0 th\u7853 t ra ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i y\u7871 u h\u417 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u?" B\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m sao gi\u7843 i th\'edch h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng t\u7889 ng c\u7893  m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i, nh\u432 ng m\u7895 i l\u7847 n v\u7915 a nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u th\'ec li\u7873 n kinh s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c th\u7853 t l\'e2u: "... Kh\'f4ng sai, \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i h\'f4m nay t\u7899 i l\'e0m phi\u7873 n c\u7853 u kia kh\'e1 y\u7871 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 g\'ec c\uc0\u361 ng l\'e0 th\u7911  l\u297 nh t\u7897 c ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i \u7903  Sophus c\'f9ng v\u7899 i chi\u7871 n lang nhanh nh\u7865 n d\u361 ng m\'e3nh nh\u7845 t, n\u7871 u nghe th\u7845 y l\u7901 i h\u7855 n \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 ch\u7855 c c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n kh\'f3c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 t\'f4i th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\u7907 i h\u7841 i h\u417 n so v\u7899 i c\u7853 u ngh\u297 ..." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n mu\u7889 n r\'e1ng b\u7893  c\u7913 u, nh\u432 ng d\u432 \u7899 i con m\u7855 t "Nh\'ecn th\u7845 u h\u7871 t th\u7843 y" c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n m\u7879 nh m\'e0 phun ra hai ch\u7919 , "M\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u r\u7845 t nhanh h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 l\u7841 i nh\u7899  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t tin t\u7913 c t\u7889 t \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t vui v\u7867  h\u417 n m\u7897 t \'edt, l\u7841 i tin t\u432 \u7903 ng n\u259 ng l\u7921 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n th\'eam m\u7897 t ch\'fat: "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, sau n\'e0y c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c s\u7907  m\u7845 y con qu\u7927  kia n\u7919 a, b\'e1o c\'e1o c\u7911 a t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7909  l\'ed, ch\u7855 c trong t\u7889 i nay s\u7869  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a \u272 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 i x\u7917  l\'fd chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  ph\u7843 i ch\u7883 u tr\u7915 ng ph\u7841 t x\u7913 ng \u273 \'e1ng. Sau n\'e0y ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi \uc0\u273 i ra ngo\'e0i s\u7855 c m\u7863 t Simon v\u7851 n lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng d\u7877  coi, h\u7855 n b\u7845 t an s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng hay s\u7855 p x\u7843 y ra, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e0n chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i \u273 \u7891 ng b\u7885 n: " Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 i theo sau Jerry kia l\'e0 ai? Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\'f4i ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p h\u7855 n \u7903  Sophus. V\u7899 i ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, n\u7871 u t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p th\'ec ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'ean."\cb1 \
\cb3 Jody l\uc0\u7849 m b\u7849 m: "Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, t\'f4i c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y bao gi\u7901 , nh\u432 ng m\'e0 kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n... Ch\'faa \u417 i, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'f3 gi\u7889 ng t\'f4i m\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c th\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7883  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ch\'fang ta tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ti\u7871 p x\'fac \u273 \u7871 n, m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 i nh\'e2n v\u7853 t." Ng\u7919  kh\'ed c\u7911 a c\'f4 \u7843  c\u361 ng \u273 \u7847 y v\u7867  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tin.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng to\'e0n b\u7897  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c th\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7883  \u7903  Sophus, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7843  ch\'e2u \'dac ch\'fang ta \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai ph\'f9 h\u7907 p h\u7871 t." M\u7897 t g\'e3 qu\u7927  kh\'e1c chen mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'ed t\uc0\u7913 c c\u7921 c m\u7841 nh thu\u7897 c v\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c th\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7883 , ho\'e0n to\'e0n xa l\u7841 , \u273 \u7841 i nh\'e2n v\u7853 t m\u7845 y ng\'e0y nay \u273 \u7871 n th\u259 m Sophus, c\'f3 li\'ean h\u7879  v\u7899 i Jerry... trong l\'f2ng Alex s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 suy \u273 o\'e1n x\u7845 u nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer?" H\u7855 n kh\u7869  phun ra c\'e1i t\'ean n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875 , Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer sao c\'f3 th\u7875  th\'e0nh b\u7897  d\u7841 ng \u273 i sau m\u7897 t nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, so v\u7899 i h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7907 ng trong l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t c\u361 ng qu\'e1 l\u7899 n r\u7891 i. H\u417 n n\u7919 a h\'ecnh nh\u432  Jerry ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t th\'e2n ph\u7853 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \'e3i h\u7855 n nh\u432  v\u7899 i b\u7841 n b\'e8 b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng." Simon c\u432 \u7901 i g\u432 \u7907 ng, "N\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng kia c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, ch\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 d\'ednh kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c th\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7883  c\u7845 p cao th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng th\u7853 t ra kh\'ed t\u7913 c \u273 \'f3 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 d\'ednh hay l\'e0 t\u7887 a ra t\u7915  b\u7843 n th\'e2n h\u7855 n v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng, n\'f3i v\u7853 y ch\u7881  v\'ec kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ho\u7863 c kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n tin t\u432 \u7903 ng, hy v\u7885 ng \u273 \'f3 ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh m\'e0 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Simon n\'f3i xong, ph\'e1t hi\uc0\u7879 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u n\'e0o ph\u7909  h\u7885 a theo m\'ecnh, nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'e1c c\u7841 nh h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t ng\u432 ng tr\u7885 ng nh\'ecn v\u7873  c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ph\'eda.\cb1 \
\cb3 Simon thu\uc0\u7853 n theo t\u7847 m m\u7855 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  nh\'ecn qua, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c m\u7903  to hai m\u7855 t, hai tay kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7897 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng th\u7889 ng nh\u7845 t m\'e0u \u273 en v\u7899 i gi\'e0y cao c\u7893  \u273 en, t\u7893 ng c\u7897 ng n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Quanh th\'e2n b\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  quanh qu\u7849 n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'ed t\u7913 c l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o v\'e0 huy\u7871 t kh\'ed nh\'e0n nh\u7841 t, nhanh ch\'f3ng l\u7845 y t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\u7851 n \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng ch\'fat c\u7843 m x\'fac l\u7841 nh nh\u432  b\u259 ng th\'f4ng b\'e1o: "Ch\'fang ta t\u7899 i t\u7915  \u272 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 y, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\'f3 v\'e0i chuy\u7879 n c\u7847 n c\'e1c ng\u432 \u417 i ph\u7889 i h\u7907 p \u273 i\u7873 u tra."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n im l\u7863 ng gi\u417  tay tr\'e1i l\'ean, b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'eda sau li\u7873 n \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7911  nhanh g\u7885 n h\u7841 n ch\u7871  h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a \u273 \'e1m Alex, d\'f9ng m\u7897 t s\u7907 i d\'e2y v\'f4 h\'ecnh tr\'f3i l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\u7895 , chu\u7849 n b\u7883  mang \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7907 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \'e3 n\'e0o...!" Simon kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng gi\'e3y tr\'e1nh ra, "C\'e1c ng\'e0i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e0m v\u7853 y v\u7899 i t\'f4i, l\'e0 qu\'fd t\u7897 c Prius \u7903  Sophus \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n \u273 \u7893 i t\'f4i th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7845 y." Trong Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u t\'e2n sinh c\'f9ng k\u7867  bi\u7871 n \u273 \u7893 i h\u7855 n c\'f3 r\'e0ng bu\u7897 c \u273 \u7863 c th\'f9, Prius r\u7845 t c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng t\u259 m v\'e0 th\u7871  l\u7921 c \u7903  Sophus, ng\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 n \u273 \u7893 i Alex v\'e0 Jody \u7903  Sophus c\u361 ng c\'f3 \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883  t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i trong Prius, cho n\'ean \u7903  Sophus b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7845 t \'edt khi c\'f3 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7889  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n g\'e2y chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\u7851 n \u273 \u7847 u \u272 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p nh\'ecn h\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Th\u7853 t sao? V\u7853 y c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 a Prius c\'f9ng \u273 \u7871 n \u272 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p lu\'f4n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Alex b\'ecnh t\uc0\u297 nh h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng l\u7847 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p. H\u7855 n nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\u7851 n \u273 \u7847 u, c\u7855 n r\u259 ng h\u7887 i: "L\'e0 ai h\u7841  l\u7879 nh mu\u7889 n \u272 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p th\u7849 m tra ch\'fang ta?"\cb1 \
