\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1m Alex s\u7869  g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng coi nh\u432  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 mang \u273 \u7871 n cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t tin t\u7913 c t\u7889 t. Hy v\u7885 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i, nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia s\u7869  b\u7883  tr\u7915 ng ph\u7841 t, t\u7915  nay v\u7873  sau m\'ecnh s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\u7919 a, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c lo s\u7907 .Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t c\u7853 u c\'f2n m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng k\'ed t\'fac \uc0\u273 \u417 n kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, b\u7903 i v\'ec ch\u7881  \u7903  m\u7897 t h\u7885 c k\u7923  v\u7843  l\u7841 i l\'fac r\u7901 i \u273 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  thanh l\'fd \u273 \u7891 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mua th\'eam \u273 \u7891  d\'f9ng trong nh\'e0, n\u417 i c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7891 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 gi\u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c gh\u7871  b\'e0n m\'e1y t\'ednh c\u7911 a k\'ed t\'fac.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7901 i v\u7883  b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u l\'e0 th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'ec ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng gh\u7871 : "Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n kia l\'e0 sao? Em kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng g\'e2y chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i h\u7885 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 l\u7855 m, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n s\u417  s\u417 ." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7849 n th\u7853 n n\'f3i, "C\'f4 b\u7841 n s\'e1t v\'e1ch ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng \u273 \'e3 c\u7913 u th\u7911  l\u297 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, l\'fac \u7845 y ch\u7855 c c\'f4 ta cho r\u7857 ng \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 s\'f3i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ho\u7863 c l\'e0 ch\'f3 c\u7905  l\u7899 n b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng. L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng c\u7843 nh b\'e1o c\'f4 ta kh\'f4ng n\'ean ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c qua l\u7841 i v\u7899 i qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, nh\u432 ng hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean c\'f4 ta kh\'f4ng nghe. M\'e0 b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'f4 ta b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\'e0m l\'e2y nhi\u7877 m, ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i kia h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 ang ngh\u297  bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p c\u7913 u c\'f4 ta, m\u432 \u7907 n c\u417  h\u7897 i n\'e0y b\'e1o \'e2n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 c\u7889  \'fd \u273 i\u7873 u tra nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  c\u7841 nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, bao g\u7891 m t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng ai l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i qua l\u7841 i th\'e2n thi\u7871 t v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, cho n\'ean bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec l\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7843 y r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u m\'e1u r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'e9p l\u7841 i r\u7845 t nhanh c\u7911 a Emily, r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng t\u7899 i m\u7913 c nguy hi\u7875 m \u273 \u7871 n t\'ednh m\u7841 ng. Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  \u273 \'f3 ch\'ednh l\'e0 l\u7901 i c\u7843 nh b\'e1o c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i?\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng vi\u7879 c \u273 \'f3 th\'ec c\'f3 quan h\u7879  g\'ec v\u7899 i em?" C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7887 i. C\u7913 u Emily v\'e0 t\u7853 p k\'edch c\u7853 u, theo l\'fd m\'e0 n\'f3i r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 hai chuy\u7879 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n ch\u7859 ng li\'ean quan.\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7859 n l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7913 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f4 b\'e9 kia, nh\u432 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  bi\u7871 t Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 ang \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, h\u417 n n\u7919 a bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f3 c\'e1ch. Nh\u432 ng ai c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t mu\u7889 n c\u7847 u Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ra tay l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n r\u7845 t kh\'f3, d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \'f4m hy v\u7885 ng g\'ec. Mu\u7889 n d\'f9ng v\u361  l\u7921 c tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p ra tay \'e9p h\u7855 n l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi li\u7871 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ngay sau \u273 \'f3 h\u417 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean d\u7901 i m\u7855 t qua ch\u7895  kh\'e1c: "... Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i \u273 \'f3 h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t v\'e0i tin t\u7913 c, c\u361 ng t\u7915  nh\u7919 ng tin t\u7913 c \u273 \'f3 suy \u273 o\'e1n c\u7853 u v\'e0 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer quan h\u7879  kh\'f4ng v\u7915 a, cho n\'ean \u273 \u7883 nh b\u7855 t c\'f3c c\u7853 u l\'e0m \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n trao \u273 \u7893 i \'e9p h\u7855 n \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng. \'dd t\'f4i l\'e0, c\'f3 l\u7869  b\u7885 n h\u7885  cho r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  d\u7877  ra tay, cho n\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm c\u7853 u g\'e2y chuy\u7879 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e0o \u273 \'e2u ra m\u7845 y tin t\u7913 c hoang \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y ch\u7913 ." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'f4m \u273 \u7847 u th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, "May m\'e0 anh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh em s\u7869  r\u7845 t th\u7843 m. Em kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer s\u7869  v\'ec em m\'e0 xu\u7845 t \u273 \u7847 u, \u273 \'f3 r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng th\u7875  b\u7883  uy hi\u7871 p, m\'e0 em \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n m\'e0 n\'f3i c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t. H\u7855 n c\'f9ng l\u7855 m ch\u7881  l\'e0 th\'edch u\u7889 ng m\'e1u c\u7911 a em th\'f4i." \u272 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 k\u7871 t c\u7909 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u r\u7845 t d\u7877  t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i l\'f2ng \u273 \u7847 y hy v\u7885 ng coi c\u7853 u l\'e0 th\u7867  \u273 \'e1nh b\u7841 c, l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\'fat gi\'e1 tr\u7883 , v\u7853 y \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i c\u7853 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 k\u7871 t qu\u7843  t\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\'f9a theo l\u7901 i c\u7853 u, ch\u7881  cam k\u7871 t: "Y\'ean t\'e2m \u273 i, t\'f4i c\u361 ng s\u7869  b\'e1o c\'e1o nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i kia. Sau n\'e0y b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7871 n qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y c\u7853 u n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i thi\'ean ph\'fa c\u7911 a ch\u7911 ng t\u7897 c, n\u259 ng l\u7921 c thu th\u7853 p v\'e0 ph\'e2n t\'edch tin t\u7913 c c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i lu\'f4n r\u7845 t m\u7841 nh, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u259 n b\u7843 n \u273 \u7873 u chu\u7849 n x\'e1c. Th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i, b\u7845 t k\'ec k\u7867  n\'e0o mi\u7877 n bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chuy\u7879 n h\u7855 n kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7845 y ng\'e0y qua, li\'ean t\u7909 c mang m\u7897 t nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'f3 \u273 o\'e1n ra Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, \'edt nh\u7845 t l\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n m\'e0 n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i kinh ng\u7841 c: "Anh c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  b\'e1o c\'e1o ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 ." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7893 i s\u7855 c n\'f3i, nghe v\'e0o tai h\u7907 p t\'ecnh h\u7907 p l\'fd nh\u432  th\u7853 t, "Tuy r\u7857 ng ch\'fang t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  ch\'ednh l\'e0 tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m qu\u7843 n ch\u7871  h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i, nh\u432 ng t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  d\'f9ng c\'e1ch n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\uc0\u7875  kh\'f4ng lau m\u7855 t m\'e0 nh\'ecn l\u7841 i v\u7883  b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7843 n th\'e2n h\u7855 n tuy r\u7857 ng n\u259 ng l\u7921 c c\'f3 h\u7841 n, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u c\'e1ch x\u7917  l\'fd, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c nh\u432  c\u7921 c k\u7923  linh th\'f4ng tin t\u7913 c, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng r\u7845 t x\'e0i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i gian \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7899 m, r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 qua m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901 , to\'e0n b\u7897  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 d\u7847 n y\'ean t\u297 nh tr\u7903  l\u7841 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi ti\u7877 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7873  th\'ec r\u7917 a m\u7863 t chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 i ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Sau khi t\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \'e8n c\u7853 u m\u417  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y trong m\u7897 ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i m\u417  th\u7845 y b\'e0n tay \u273 \'f3. C\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng th\u7903  d\u7889 c, than nh\u7865  truy \u273 u\u7893 i theo \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a b\'e0n tay kia, kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i... To\'e0n b\u7897  c\u7843 nh trong m\u417  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\'e0u \u273 en, say ng\u7885 t m\'e0 qu\u7845 n qu\'fdt tri\u7873 n mi\'ean, l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  n\u7893 i m\'e0 tr\u7847 m lu\'e2n trong \u273 \'f3. T\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y r\'f5 b\u7897  d\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 nh cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng trong m\u417 , c\u7853 u r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e0n tay kia \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u \u273 \u7855 c \'fd c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7929  m\'e3n m\'e0 c\u432 \u7901 i, ngay c\u7843  c\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng th\u7903  g\u7845 p, c\u7847 m b\'e0n tay \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e8 l\'ean ng\u7921 c, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  n\'f3 t\'e1c qu\'e1i kh\u7855 p n\u417 i tr\'ean c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh, c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  n\'f3 r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i. Sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean tinh t\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7845 y r\'f5 b\'e0n tay kia\'97\'97 tr\u7855 ng nh\u7907 t, thon d\'e0i, h\u7919 u l\u7921 c, tr\'ean ng\'f3n \'e1p \'fat tay tr\'e1i \u273 eo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n m\'e0u b\u7841 c d\'e0y. B\u7873  m\u7863 t nh\u7851 n c\'f3 kh\u7855 c hoa v\u259 n tinh x\u7843 o m\'e0 b\'ed hi\u7875 m, b\u7909 i gai r\u7853 m v\u432 \u417 n th\u7859 ng l\'ean tr\u7901 i, ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a b\u7909 i gai qu\u7845 n ch\u7863 t m\u7897 t b\'f4ng h\u7891 ng m\u7843 nh mai...\cb1 \
