\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u7843 o n\'e3o b\'f2 d\u7853 y u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o, c\u7847 m kh\u259 n m\u7863 t lau m\u7891  h\'f4i, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7855 p ch\u259 n l\u7847 n n\u7919 a. Hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  ban \u273 \'eam Sophus \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\u7841 nh, k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 v\u7851 n ch\u432 a c\'f3 l\'f2 s\u432 \u7903 i, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\u7841 nh, nh\u432 ng v\'ec gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng n\'e0y, c\u7853 u r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ra m\u7897 t th\'e2n m\u7891  h\'f4i.\cb1 \
