\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i tr\u7903  th\'e0nh s\u7921  th\u7853 t r\u7891 i sao? Nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\u7885  th\u7853 t s\u7921  b\u7883  mang \u273 i ch\u7883 u tr\u7915 ng ph\u7841 t r\u7891 i? Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi nghe xong \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  \u273 \'f3, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 Julia c\'f2n t\uc0\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u l\'e0 v\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u417  h\u7897 i n\'f3i ch\'e0o t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t v\u7899 i h\'e0ng x\'f3m m\'e0 ti\u7871 c nu\u7889 i, h\u7843 o t\'e2m an \u7911 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7915 a c\u417  h\u7887 i th\u259 m t\'ecnh h\'ecnh Emily. C\'f4 Julia tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "Kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t l\u7855 m. H\'f4m qua l\'fac t\'f4i r\u7901 i \u273 i v\u7851 n \u273 ang c\'e1ch ly quan s\'e1t, d\'f9ng thu\u7889 c an th\u7847 n li\u7873 u m\u7841 nh m\u7899 i an t\u297 nh l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, m\u7845 u ch\u7889 t l\'e0 b\'e1c s\u297  kh\'f4ng tra ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f4 b\'e9 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 b\u7883  l\'e0m sao, kh\'f4ng ai bi\u7871 t nguy\'ean nh\'e2n t\u7841 i sao c\'f4 b\'e9 \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean m\u7845 t tr\'ed."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 th\uc0\u432 \u417 ng c\u7843 m nh\'ecn c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean t\'f3c \u273 en c\'f3 h\'e0ng x\'f3m xung quanh l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng may n\'e0y: "Th\u7843  l\u7887 ng \u273 i, ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 c\u7911 a c\'f4 b\'e9 \u273 ang \u7903  c\'f9ng r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n r\'f5 r\u7879 t li\'ean h\u7879  gi\u7919 a th\u7871  gi\u7899 i th\u7921 c t\u7841 i v\u7899 i th\u7871  gi\u7899 i trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7921 a theo l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Alex l\'e0 b\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c mang \u273 i th\u7849 m tra, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c th\u7911  t\u7909 c v\u7899 i t\u432  c\'e1ch nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n g\u7885 n gh\u7869  r\'f5 r\'e0ng, m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\u7917  l\'fd \u7893 n th\u7887 a, t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i quen bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7901 i gi\u7843 i th\'edch h\u7907 p l\'fd, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai c\u7843 m th\u7845 y k\u7923  qu\'e1i, n\'f3 b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng ai ch\'fa \'fd. Ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t n\u7897 i t\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 s\u7889 ng h\u417 n tr\u259 m n\u259 m.\cb1 \
