\cb3 N\uc0\u259 m ng\'e0y sau Emily tr\u7903  l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0 k\'fd t\'fac. Xem ra m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a c\'f4 \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 \u7893 n, kh\'ed s\u7855 c kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , c\'f9ng b\u7841 n m\'ecnh l\'e0m vi\u7879 c m\'e0 trong m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7853 u coi l\'e0 "Ng\u7847 m x\u7917  l\'fd", \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n Alex v\'e0 \u273 \u7891 ng b\u7885 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  hi\u7879 n qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u c\u7843 m x\'fac kinh ng\u7841 c.\cb1 \
