\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec th\'f4i, nh\u432 ng nh\u7919 ng gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng kia l\u7841 i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'f4ng. Li\'ean t\u7909 c n\u259 m ng\'e0y, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u7903  trong m\u7897 ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u v\'f4 c\'f9ng th\'e2n m\u7853 t, h\u417 n n\u7919 a n\u7897 i dung c\u7843 nh trong m\u417  c\u361 ng c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng s\'e2u... Th\u7853 m ch\'ed m\u7895 i chi ti\u7871 t m\u7895 i \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u v\'f4 c\'f9ng r\'f5 n\'e9t v\'f4 c\'f9ng ch\'e2n th\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7847 m m\u7915 ng r\u7857 ng sau h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 m\'ecnh v\u7851 n ch\u432 a g\u7863 p l\u7841 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, v\u7851 n ch\u7881  li\'ean l\u7841 c th\'f4ng qua \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\'e0 tin nh\u7855 n nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia. Th\u7871  nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  c\u7847 n nghe th\u7845 y gi\u7885 ng h\u7855 n c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean, b\'ean kia n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n nghi\'eam ch\u7881 nh, v\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c ho\u7863 c v\u7873  ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i, l\u7841 i nh\u7855 c c\u7853 u t\u7921  b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\u7889 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n, c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 th\u7845 t th\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7891 n v\'eda l\'ean m\'e2y xong ho\'e0n v\u7873  r\u7891 i m\u7899 i kinh s\u7907  b\u7843 n th\'e2n nghe gi\u7885 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e0 l\u7841 i suy ngh\u297  m\u7845 y th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'f3, hai m\'e1 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c n\'f3ng l\'ean, b\u7909 ng \u273 \u7847 y h\u7893  th\u7865 n. \u7902  trong \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u361 ng ch\u7881  \u7853 m \u7915  cho c\'f3, m\u7897 t c\'e2u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh \u273 \'fang l\'e0 m\u7845 t tr\'ed r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y Emily tr\uc0\u7903  v\u7873  l\'e0 th\u7913  b\u7843 y, t\u7845 t c\u7843  b\u7841 n h\u7885 c \u7903  t\u7847 ng b\u7889 n v\'ec \u273 \u7875  \u259 n m\u7915 ng c\'f4 b\u7841 n kh\u7887 i h\u7859 n m\'e0 \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t t\u7893  ch\u7913 c m\u7897 t b\u7919 a ti\u7879 c nh\u7887 . N\'f3i th\u7853 t, l\'fac Emily ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh, b\u7897  d\'e1ng \u273 \'f3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  d\u7885 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7843 y d\u7921 ng, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7913 ng ki\u7871 n l\'fac \u7845 y cho \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  v\u7851 n c\'f2n s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7897 i dung b\u7919 a ti\u7879 c l\'e0 m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m m\u7897 t m\'f3n s\u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  c\'f9ng nhau \u259 n. T\u7847 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m pizza, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u432 \u7899 ng b\'e1nh chocolate, b\u7841 n h\u7885 c ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7844 n v\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i Malaysia chia nhau l\'e0m \u273 \u7891  \u259 n c\u7911 a n\u432 \u7899 c m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin n\'e0y c\u361 ng ng\u7849 n ra, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\'e0o \u273 \'f3n Emily tr\u7903  v\u7873 , th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 v\'ec b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng l\'e0m n\u7893 i m\'f3n g\'ec. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh r\u7911  Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 i theo, b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'ec \u273 i si\'eau th\u7883  mua c\'e1nh g\'e0, c\'e0 r\u7889 t, l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n hi\u7879 u th\u7883 t Trung Qu\u7889 c mua th\u7883 t ba ch\u7881 , m\u7901 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n l\'e0m ba t\'f4 c\'e1nh g\'e0 v\'e0 m\u7897 t t\'f4 th\u7883 t kho t\'e0u, \u259 n c\'f9ng b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7919 a t\u7889 i v\u7851 n r\u7845 t vui v\u7867 , Giang \u272 i\u7873 n l\'e0m hai m\'f3n \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  hoan ngh\'eanh nh\u7845 t tr\'ed. Caroline b\u7841 n c\u7911 a Emily v\'e0 c\'f4 Julia c\u361 ng t\u7899 i tham gia, c\'f4 n\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7897 t m\'e2m b\'e1nh quy l\u7899 n, tr\'ean b\'e1nh c\'f3 vi\u7871 t l\u7901 i ch\'fac ph\'fac t\u7899 i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Caroline c\uc0\u7843 m \u417 n c\'e1c b\u7841 n h\u7885 c t\u7847 ng b\u7889 n, c\'f2n \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t c\u7843 m \u417 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 c\'f4 Julia: "\u272 \'eam \u273 \'f3 l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u Emily ch\u7881  h\u417 i s\u7889 t nh\u7865 , b\u7841 n \u7845 y n\'f3i trong ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, em v\u7851 n \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng c\'f9ng b\u7841 n \u7845 y, ai ng\u7901  Emily \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean h\'f4n m\'ea, l\'fac t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i th\'ec \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t tr\'ed, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n mu\u7889 n c\u7855 n em." N\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y c\'f4 c\u7889  \'fd d\'f9ng bi\u7875 u t\'ecnh khoa tr\u432 \u417 ng li\u7871 c Emily, t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'ec c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "May m\'e0 c\'f3 m\uc0\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  tr\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng b\u7841 n \u7845 y, c\'f2n g\u7885 i xe c\u7913 u th\u432 \u417 ng, c\u361 ng may l\'e0 c\'f3 c\'f4 Julia \u273 i vi\u7879 n c\'f9ng Emily, l\'fac \u7845 y em \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1 s\u7907  h\'e3i. C\u7843 m \u417 n c\u7843  Jerry \u273 \'e3 gi\'fap m\'ecnh tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Emily c\uc0\u361 ng theo Caroline m\'e0 bi\u7875 u \u273 \u7841 t l\'f2ng c\u7843 m k\'edch v\u7899 i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, k\u7875  c\u7843  c\'f4 b\u7841 n n\'e0y c\u361 ng cho r\u7857 ng Emily ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean v\'ec ph\'e1t s\u7889 t m\'e0 sinh ra m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n qu\'e1i b\u7879 nh, b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n b\'ean kia \u273 \u432 a ra l\u7901 i gi\u7843 i th\'edch "Nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  cao d\u7851 n \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7845 t \u273 i\u7879 n gi\u7843 i r\u7889 i lo\u7841 n" . S\u7869  kh\'f4ng ai ngh\u297  t\u7899 i nguy\'ean nh\'e2n d\'e2y m\u417  r\u7877  m\'e1 r\u7889 i r\u7855 m gi\u7919 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u v\'e0 chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ai bi\u7871 t nguy\'ean nh\'e2n th\u7921 c s\u7921  ph\'eda sau \u273 \u7841 i n\u7841 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a c\'f4.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u258 n xong m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng nhau thu d\u7885 n b\'e1t \u273 \u361 a v\'e0 \u273 \u7893  r\'e1c, sau \u273 \'f3 ai n\u7845 y \u273 \u7873 u t\u7921  m\'ecnh r\u7901 i \u273 i l\'e0m vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Giang \u272 i\u7873 n h\'e0o h\u7913 ng t\u259 ng v\u7885 t, v\u7851 n ch\u432 a mu\u7889 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, h\'e0o h\u7913 ng b\u7915 ng b\u7915 ng l\'f4i k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7873  ph\'f2ng c\'f9ng h\u7855 n ch\u417 i b\u7897  game m\u7899 i mua.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 ch\u417 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901 , game \u273 \'e3 qua hai c\u7917 a, \u272 \u7897 t nhi\'ean Giang \u272 i\u7873 n gi\u7885 ng bu\u7891 n b\u7921 c n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\'c0i, Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , t\'f4i kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 e l\u7855 m, \u273 \u7847 u h\u417 i v\'e1ng r\u7891 i. T\'f4i \u273 i ngh\u7881  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y, c\u7853 u c\u7913  ch\u417 i ti\u7871 p \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn qua, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y Giang \u272 i\u7873 n m\u7863 t \u273 \u7887  ng\u7847 u, l\'fac \u273 ang ch\u417 i game c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y m\u7863 t Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \u7887  l\'ean, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, ch\u7881  cho l\'e0 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n ch\u417 i game qu\'e1 k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng, gi\u7901  nh\'ecn k\u7929  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y r\'f5 m\u7863 t b\u7841 n m\'ecnh \u273 \u7887  \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u7887 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "\u272 \u7841 i Giang c\u7853 u sao th\u7871 ? Sao m\u7863 t \u273 \u7887  v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n c\u361 ng l\u7845 y tay xoa m\u7863 t m\'ecnh, cau m\'e0y n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  l\'e0 bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i \u259 n nhi\u7873 u qu\'e1? H\u417 i n\'f3ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7909  nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  trong ph\'f2ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, l\u7841 i nh\'ecn \'e1o ph\'f4ng c\u7897 c tay tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n: " \u272 \u7841 i Giang n\'e0y, c\u7853 u m\u7863 c th\'eam \u273 \u7891  v\'e0o \u273 i, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i b\u7883  s\u7889 t r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 nhi\u7879 t k\u7871  kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Hi\uc0\u7879 n gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 g\u7847 n gi\u7919 a th\'e1ng t\u432 , tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m Sophus l\u7841 nh nh\u7845 t nh\u432 ng l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 b\u7885 n c\u7853 u l\u7841 nh nh\u7845 t, nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  \u273 \'e3 h\u7841 , th\u7871  nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ch\u432 a c\'f3 l\'f2 s\u432 \u7903 i. Ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  b\'ean m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 n\u7855 ng, m\'f9a h\'e8 trong ph\'f2ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t m\'e1t m\u7867 , th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y th\'ec \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o, l\u7841 i c\'f2n v\u7915 a m\u432 a xong. Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u7927  v\'e0o b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\'f2n tr\u7867  kh\u7887 e, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y ch\u7881  m\u7863 c \'e1o ng\u7855 n tay trong ph\'f2ng, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c d\u7877  sinh b\u7879 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7901  Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 n\u7857 m l\'ec tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, tr\'f9m k\'edn ch\u259 n, nh\'ecn qua c\'f3 v\u7867  nh\u432  trong th\u7901 i gian ng\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  n\'ean kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u. H\u7855 n u\u7875  o\u7843 i n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "D\u432 \u7899 i b\'e0n \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n ng\u259 n k\'e9o th\u7913  hai, b\'ean trong c\'f3 m\u7897 t h\u7897 p gi\u7845 y \u273 \'e8 tr\'ean h\'f2m thu\u7889 c, nhi\u7879 t k\u7871  \u7903  b\'ean ph\u7843 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  ng\u259 n k\'e9o \u273 \u432 a tay s\u7901 , qu\u7843  nhi\'ean nhi\u7879 t k\u7871  c\'f3 \u7903  \u273 \'f3. C\u7853 u l\u7845 y ra \u273 \u432 a cho Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, \u273 \u7875  Giang \u272 i\u7873 n t\u7921  \u273 o nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897 , b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'ec c\u7847 m c\u7889 c c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i l\u7845 y n\u432 \u7899 c \u7845 m cho h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac c\u7853 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i th\'ec Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 k\u7865 p nhi\u7879 t k\u7871  ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \'e1nh th\u7913 c h\u7855 n, \u273 \u7875  c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c qua m\u7897 t b\'ean r\u7891 i t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\u7845 y nhi\u7879 t k\u7871 , \u273 \u7875  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn th\u7917  \'97\'97 ba m\u432 \u417 i t\'e1m \u273 \u7897 . Tuy r\u7857 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng ch\u7913 ng t\u7887  l\'e0 ph\'e1t s\u7889 t, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7899 i m\u7913 c ph\u7843 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u432 a \u273 i vi\u7879 n, nh\u7919 ng l\'fac nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c h\u7841  s\u7889 t th\u7917 , n\u7871 u nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  cao kh\'f4ng gi\u7843 m th\'ec s\u7869  c\'e2n nh\u7855 c chuy\u7879 n \u273 i vi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n s\u7855 p x\u7871 p r\u7845 t quy c\u7911 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7845 t nhanh l\u7841 i t\'ecm ra thu\u7889 c h\u7841  s\u7889 t trong h\'f2m thu\u7889 c, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7905  Giang \u272 i\u7873 n ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, c\u7847 m c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c v\u7915 a l\u7845 y \u273 \u432 a cho h\u7855 n u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c, l\u7841 i \u273 \u7905  h\u7855 n n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng. L\'e0m xong xu\'f4i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i m\'e0 ng\u7891 i \u7903  gh\u7871  ch\u7901 . N\u7871 u m\u7897 t l\'e1t n\u7919 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng h\u7841  s\u7889 t, c\u7853 u s\u7869  ph\u7843 i \u273 \u432 a h\u7855 n \u273 i vi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u273 \u7885 c b\'e1o hai m\u432 \u417 i ph\'fat, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c Giang \u272 i\u7873 n gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t, trong mi\u7879 ng c\u361 ng ph\'e1t ra m\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng l\u7849 m b\u7849 m kh\'f4ng r\'f5. C\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng: "Sao th\u7871 ? Kh\'e1 h\u417 n ch\'fat n\'e0o ch\u432 a? Mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 mu\u7889 n \u273 o l\u7841 i nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong gi\'e2y l\'e1t Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n l\u7841 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ng\u7891 i b\u7853 t d\u7853 y th\u7859 ng t\u7855 p, nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 \u432 a tay ra s\u7913 c si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t c\'e1nh tay ph\u7843 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng h\'e1 m\u7891 m mu\u7889 n c\u7855 n c\u7893  tay c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7913 c h\u7855 n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tr\u7903  n\'ean r\u7845 t m\u7841 nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'fac nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng gi\'e3y ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'eau t\'ean h\u7855 n, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fat ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n thanh minh nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 \u7909 c ng\u7847 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7855 p ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh th\u7871  c\u7845 p b\'e1ch, Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'f9ng tay tr\'e1i c\u7847 m chi\u7871 c \'e1o c\u7897 c tay \u273 \u7863 t b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n nh\'e9t th\u7859 ng v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. D\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 \u273 \u7891  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, ch\u7855 c Giang \u272 i\u7873 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd. Giang \u272 i\u7873 n c\u7855 n \'e1o m\u7897 t c\'e1i, trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t h\u417 i gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y tr\uc0\u7921 c gi\'e1c Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\'e2n c\u417  h\u7897 i n\'e0y nhanh ch\'f3ng tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i tr\'f3i bu\u7897 c c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng ra kh\u7887 i ph\'f2ng, kh\'f3a ch\u7863 t c\u7917 a l\u7841 i. \u272 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c d\'f9ng \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\u7849 n c\u7845 p trong h\'e0nh lang g\u7885 i cho c\'f4 Julia, k\'eau c\'f4 v\'e0 nh\'e2n vi\'ean kh\'e1c trong k\'fd t\'fac t\u7899 i gi\'fap ch\u259 m s\'f3c Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i nh\u7901  g\u7885 i gi\'fap xe c\u7913 u th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hi\uc0\u7879 n gi\u7901  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  n\u7893 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, m\'e0 b\u7897  d\u7841 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7911 a Giang \u272 i\u7873 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng cho th\u7845 y \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t tr\'ed, th\u7853 m ch\'ed b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng x\'f4 c\u7917 a "R\u7847 m r\u7847 m" truy\u7873 n ra t\u7915  trong ph\'f2ng h\u7855 n, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng nhanh g\u7885 i b\'e1c s\u297  \u273 \u7871 n, coi ch\u7915 ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n s\u7869  l\'e0m b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng ch\'ednh h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y b\uc0\u7841 n h\u7885 c l\u7847 u hai nghe th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh c\u361 ng nhao nhao \u273 i ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7915 ng t\u7899 i g\u7847 n." Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u259 n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang \u273 \u7883 nh t\u7899 i g\u7847 n, "V\u7915 a r\u7891 i Kevin b\u7883  s\u7889 t, \'fd th\u7913 c kh\'f4ng t\u7881 nh t\'e1o l\u7855 m, b\'e2y gi\u7901  h\'e0nh vi h\u417 i h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n, t\'f4i s\u7907  c\u7853 u ta s\u7869  l\'e0m b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ho\u7863 c ch\'ednh m\'ecnh, n\'ean ch\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'e3 r\u7891 i h\'e3y t\'ednh."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\'faa \uc0\u417 i." M\u7897 t b\u7841 n n\u7919  th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng h\'f4 l\'ean, "B\u7897  d\u7841 ng nh\'ecn gi\u7889 ng Emily l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c qu\'e1. Th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  Emily v\u7915 a tr\u7903  v\u7873  Kevin l\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c t\'e2m m\'ecnh n\u7863 ng n\u7873  suy s\u7909 p, kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t. L\u7901 i Caroline n\'f3i tr\'ean b\'e0n c\u417 m khi n\'e3y quanh qu\u7849 n b\'ean tai. L\'fac v\u7915 a th\u7845 y Giang \u272 i\u7873 n bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 d\u7921  c\u7843 m n\'e0y, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  ch\u7859 ng qua l\'e0 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c n\'f3i ra mi\u7879 ng m\'e0 th\'f4i \'97\'97 c\'e1i d\u7841 ng kia, qu\'e1 gi\u7889 ng v\u7899 i Emily l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 n n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng ai bi\u7871 t r\'f5 h\u417 n c\u7853 u, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7841 i c\u7853 u ngu ng\u7889 c mang b\u7841 n \u273 i tham gia y\u7871 n h\u7897 i m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7855 n trong \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh. H\u417 n n\u7919 a r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 b\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p th\u7845 p c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng g\'e2y l\'e2y nhi\u7877 m cao m\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i c\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ai bi\uc0\u7871 t ng\'e0y tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e1nh b\u7883  nhi\u7877 m \u273 \'f3, th\u7901 i k\u7923  \u7911  b\u7879 nh d\'e0i bao nhi\'eau?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 au kh\u7893  \'f4m tr\'e1n. C\u7853 u t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng sau khi c\u7853 u v\'e0 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \u7841 t th\'e0nh \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh kia, mang b\u7841 n m\'ecnh b\'ecnh an tr\u7903  v\u7873  v\u7853 y l\'e0 xong; c\u7853 u cho r\u7857 ng sau chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n k\u7871 t th\'fac, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh g\u7863 p con qu\u7927  kia l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e2u ai ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n \'e1c qu\u7927  s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 gieo h\u7841 t gi\u7889 ng t\'e0n kh\u7889 c xu\u7889 ng, kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p nh\u7919 ng ph\'e0m nh\'e2n v\'f4 n\u259 ng nh\u432  b\u7885 n h\u7885  tr\u7889 n ch\u7841 y n\u7917 a b\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t nhanh c\'f4 Julia v\'e0 nh\'e2n vi\'ean y t\u7871  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i, b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0m gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Emily l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, tr\'f3i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n tr\'ean c\'e1ng, mang l\'ean xe c\u7913 u th\u432 \u417 ng. Suy t\'ednh \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c Giang \u272 i\u7873 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 c\'f4 Julia c\'f9ng \u273 i theo t\u7899 i b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 Julia nh\uc0\u7865  gi\u7885 ng an \u7911 i c\u7853 u: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'e2u, tuy r\u7857 ng tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn h\u417 i d\u7885 a ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng Kevin nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  kh\u7887 e l\u7841 i r\u7845 t nhanh gi\u7889 ng Emily."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\u7863 n ra n\u7893 i m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng. C\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\'f2ng m\'ecnh tr\u7903  n\'ean th\u7853 t n\u7863 ng n\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 nh\u7845 t, Emily m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 d\u7877  d\'e0ng kh\u7887 e l\u7841 i. Th\u7911  l\u297 nh t\u7897 c ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i \u7903  Sophus \u273 \'e3 hao ph\'ed r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u c\'f4ng s\u7913 c m\u7899 i m\u7901 i m\u7897 t v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, nh\u7901  v\u7853 y m\u7899 i c\u7913 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7841 ng c\'f4.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng cho l\'e0 m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7871  l\u7921 c v\'e0 m\u7841 ng l\u432 \u7899 i quan h\u7879  t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Baird kia; c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng cho r\u7857 ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p c\u7913 u th\u7911  l\u297 nh sinh v\u7853 t h\u7855 c \'e1m l\u7907 i h\u7841 i n\'e0o \u273 \'f3, h\u417 n n\u7919 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f2n nh\u7899  k\u7929  mu\u7889 n b\'e1o \u417 n. Hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i Baird Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng v\u7889 n \u273 ang \u273 i ngh\u7881  \u7903  New Zealand, nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7901 i th\u7881 nh c\u7847 u c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i n\'ean m\u7899 i t\u7841 m d\u7915 ng ch\'e2n \u7903  Sophus, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\'f3 l\u7869  h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u7903  Sophus r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  th\u7921 c ra c\u361 ng c\'f2n m\u7897 t v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'f3 \u7903  Sophus, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u7853 u c\'f2n v\u7915 a v\u7863 n quen bi\u7871 t. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i m\u7901 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ra tay l\'e0 m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 t c\u7921 c k\u7923  kh\'f3 kh\u259 n. K\u7923  th\u7853 t nh\'ecn t\u7897 c ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i l\'e0 bi\u7871 t, b\u7885 n h\u7885  th\'e0 quanh co l\'f2ng v\'f2ng \u273 i c\u7847 u Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Baird \u273 i ngang qua ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng th\u7917  \u273 i nh\u7901  c\u7853 y Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer hi\u7879 n \u273 ang ngh\u7881  l\'e2u d\'e0i \u7903  Sophus.\cb1 \
\cb3 Vi\uc0\u7879 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7911  \u273 \u7875  cho th\u7845 y v\u7883  kia \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kh\'f3 d\'e2y v\'e0o v\u7843  l\u7841 i kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  giao thi\u7879 p c\u7905  n\'e0o. Th\u7853 m ch\'ed \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\u7841 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 \uc0\u273 \'e3 b\u7883  h\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u ba l\u7847 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng \u273 o\'e1n ra t\'ednh t\'ecnh c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng \u273 o\'e1n ra s\u7903  th\'edch v\'e0 \'fd mu\u7889 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 Julia \uc0\u273 i h\u7895  tr\u7907  l\'e0m c\'e1c th\u7911  t\u7909 c, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n b\u7883  mang \u273 i ki\u7875 m tra c\'e1c m\u7909 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7915 a c\u417  \u273 i v\'e0o m\u7897 t g\'f3c b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n \u7845 n g\u7885 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Hai tay c\u7853 u h\u417 i run, trong ng\u7921 c \u7849 n \u7849 n mang ch\'fat hi v\u7885 ng tha thi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng r\'f5 \'97\'97 n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t lu\u7853 n n\'f3i th\u7871  n\'e0o, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n nghe \'fd ki\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n l\'e0 th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  c\'f3 ch\u7911  \'fd g\'ec \u273 \'f3? D\'f9 sao h\u7855 n v\u7851 n hi\u7875 u bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y h\u417 n m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 \'e3 l\'e0 m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean g\u7917 i th\u7917  cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t tin nh\u7855 n "\u272 \'e3 ng\u7911  ch\u432 a? Em mu\u7889 n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i anh" . Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng h\u7891 i \'e2m m\'e0 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7889  gi\u7919  gi\u7885 ng b\'ecnh t\u297 nh k\u7875  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n x\u7843 y ra t\u7889 i nay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe c\u7853 u k\u7875  xong im l\u7863 ng r\u7845 t l\'e2u, n\u7917 a ng\'e0y sau m\u7899 i n\'f3i: "Xin l\u7895 i, A Di\'ean, l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u r\u7891 i, t\'f4i b\u7845 t l\u7921 c. C\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y ng\u432 \u7901 i duy nh\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 c\'e1ch l\'e0 ai m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kinh ng\uc0\u7841 c \'f4m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ng\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7907 t xu\u7889 ng, hai m\u7855 t m\u7901  m\u7883 t nh\'ecn b\u7891 n hoa xanh m\'e1t trong g\'f3c, tia hy v\u7885 ng v\u7851 n \'f4m l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c gi\u7901  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  c\u7855 t \u273 \u7913 t. Tuy r\u7857 ng s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t hy v\u7885 ng xa v\u7901 i, nh\u432 ng l\'e0 con ng\u432 \u7901 i, d\'f9 sao v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i c\'f3 k\u7923  t\'edch, hy v\u7885 ng m\'ecnh s\u7869  ch\'ednh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i may m\u7855 n \u273 \'f3, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c n\'f3i cho m\'ecnh bi\u7871 t, hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c ch\'ednh l\'e0 hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh mu\uc0\u7889 n em \u273 i c\u7847 u Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer? N\u7871 u h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u ra tay c\u7913 u Giang \u272 i\u7873 n th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o? Mu\u7889 n em... nh\'ecn c\u7853 u \u7845 y bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7899  ng\u7849 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y sao?" Gi\u7885 ng c\u7853 u l\u7897  ra kh\u7893  s\u7903  v\'e0 b\u7845 t an kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  che gi\u7845 u, \'fd ngh\u297  cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi..." C\u7853 u th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng, kh\u7849 n thi\u7871 t g\u7885 i t\'ean h\u7855 n, mang theo ch\'fat c\u7847 u xin.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u c\u7913  th\u7917  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n \u273 i." Thanh \'e2m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\'f4 c\'f9ng nh\u7865 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\u7901 i n\u7881  non c\u7911 a t\'ecnh nh\'e2n, "C\u7853 u th\u7917  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n xem, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer... C\'f3 l\u7869  h\u7855 n s\u7869  m\u7873 m l\'f2ng v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7915 ng kh\u7893  s\u7903  n\u7919 a. Su\'fdt ch\'fat n\u7919 a th\'f4i ta \u273 \'e3 mu\u7889 n b\u7845 t ch\u7845 p t\u7845 t c\u7843 , ho\'e0n to\'e0n th\u7887 a hi\u7879 p v\u7899 i em r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
