\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7847 u h\u7855 n, g\u7847 n nh\u432  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c mu\u7889 n l\'e0m c\u7853 u y\'ean t\'e2m kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i s\u7907  n\u7919 a, nhanh ch\'f3ng d\u7913 t kho\'e1t \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng s\u7869  gi\'fap, nh\u432 ng ngay tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng l\u7841 i nh\u7899  t\u7899 i l\u7901 i m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i\'97\'97 "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o, nh\u432 ng ch\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ch\u7855 c s\u7869  c\'f3 c\'e1ch..." .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, l\'fac n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng t\u7841 m th\u7901 i thay \u273 \u7893 i g\'f3c nh\'ecn.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng nh\u7899  r\'f5 l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u7853 u y\'ean l\u7863 ng m\u7897 t l\'e1t, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Nh\u432 ng tu\u7847 n n\'e0y h\u7855 n m\u7899 i ch\u7881  g\u7885 i em t\u7899 i h\'fat m\'e1u m\u7897 t l\u7847 n. Em kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao \u273 \u7875  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7855 n." Th\u7913  s\'e1u tu\u7847 n n\'e0y c\'e1ch \u273 \'e2y hai ng\'e0y Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer m\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n h\'fat m\'e1u m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7847 n nh\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t h\u7913 ng th\'fa \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\'e1u m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngay b\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  ta c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i \u273 \'f3n em.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  m\'e0 nu\u7889 t nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y xu\u7889 ng: "Ch\u7855 c c\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ch\u7913 ? Lo\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ph\u7843 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 i t\'ecm h\u7855 n. B\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\'e2y nhi\u7877 m kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\'ec ho\'e3n, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i ch\u7919 a trong b\u7843 y hai ti\u7871 ng m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, n\u7871 u nh\u432  qua b\u7843 y hai ti\u7871 ng, d\'f9 c\'f3 l\'e0 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ch\u7881  s\u7907  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  c\u7913 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7841 n c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7843 m \u417 n, sau \u273 \'f3 c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i. C\u7853 u nh\'ecn c\u7843 nh \u273 \'eam t\u7889 i m\u7883 t ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n, c\u7847 m di \u273 \u7897 ng, trong l\'f2ng \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'eau c\'f4 Julia \uc0\u273 i v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i, tr\u7843  l\u7901 i m\u7845 y tin nh\u7855 n h\u7887 i th\u259 m t\'ecnh h\'ecnh Giang \u272 i\u7873 n c\u7911 a b\u7841 n b\'e8 th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f9ng nhau \u259 n trong k\'ed t\'fac, l\u7841 i giao h\u7865 n v\u7899 i l\'e3o Cao b\u7843 o b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\'e1ng mai t\u7899 i thay ca ch\u259 m s\'f3c Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u226 \u768 m \u273 i\'ea\u803 n thoa\u803 i v\'e0o trang web c\u7911 a taxi \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u417 ng \u7903  Sophus h\u7865 n t\'e1m gi\u7901  s\'e1ng mai t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n m\'ecnh. \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\u7889  Sophus r\u7845 t \'edt xe, xe taxi c\'f2n \'edt h\u417 n, mu\u7889 n b\u7855 t xe c\u417  b\u7843 n ph\u7843 i h\u7865 n tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'f3m l\'e3o Cao kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ti\u7871 t s\'e1ng h\'f4m sau, b\u7843 y gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i thay ca cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng ch\u7907 p m\u7855 t, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tr\'ec ho\'e3n n\u7919 a, d\u7863 n d\'f2 b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\'e0i c\'e2u t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, ch\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n t\'e1m gi\u7901  xe taxi c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 h\u7865 n t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n li\u7873 n l\'ean xe r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng quay v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i h\u7885 c m\'e0 tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p k\'eau t\'e0i x\u7871  \u273 i v\u7873  ngo\u7841 i \'f4 ph\'eda t\'e2y. Grey \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng l\'e1i xe \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u \u273 i \u273 i v\u7873  v\u7873  hai l\u7847 n, v\u7853 y n\'ean c\u7853 u nh\u7899  mang m\'e1ng v\u7883  tr\'ed trang vi\'ean c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f2a nh\'e0 tr\uc0\u7847 m l\u7863 ng \u273 \u7913 ng s\u7915 ng s\u7919 ng r\u7845 t d\u7877  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c ch\'fa \'fd, sau khi ch\u7841 y ra ngoa\u803 i \'f4 ph\'eda t\'e2y th\'e0nh ph\u7889 , v\u432 \u7907 t qua hai con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng quanh co \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y, n\'f3 nh\u432  con th\'fa l\u7899 n ch\u7901  c\u7853 u chui \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o l\u432 \u7899 i, cho d\'f9 d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i bu\u7893 i s\u7899 m s\'e1ng r\u7905  chi\u7871 u xu\u7889 ng v\u7851 n h\u417 i u \'e1m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7845 y m\u7915 ng v\'ec c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n v\u7873  ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u432 \u7899 ng v\'e0 tr\'ed nh\u7899  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng t\u7879  l\u7855 m, d\u7921 a v\'e0o \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng trong \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f2a trang vi\'ean thu\u7897 c v\u7873  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer kia. C\u7853 u thanh to\'e1n ti\u7873 n xe xong n\'f3i t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t v\u7899 i t\'e0i x\u7871 , xu\u7889 ng xe h\'edt s\'e2u m\u7897 t h\u417 i, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u quan s\'e1t tr\u7901 i thu Sophus s\'e1ng s\u7899 m xanh bi\u7871 c thanh m\'e1t, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda c\'e1nh c\u7893 ng l\u7899 n s\u7853 m m\'e0u b\'ean kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 l\u7869  m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac, suy cho c\'f9ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 9h s\'e1ng, l\'e0 th\u7901 i gian ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7901 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng l\u7841 i l\'e0 th\u7901 i gian ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i c\u7911 a ng\'e0i qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Song c\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng qu\u7843 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nhi\u7873 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 i th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n b\u7853 c thang nh\u7845 n chu\'f4ng c\u7917 a. N\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7875  \'fd, v\u7853 y c\u7853 u c\u7913  an v\u7883  \u7903  tr\'ean b\u7853 c thang ch\u7901  l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. D\u7921 a v\'e0o kinh nghi\u7879 m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng qua bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  kia s\u7869  b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng. N\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac h\u7855 n v\u7851 n mu\u7889 n \u259 n ch\'fat g\'ec \u273 \'f3. Hy v\u7885 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng con ng\u432 \u7901 i, sau khi \u259 n u\u7889 ng no \u273 \u7911  s\u7869  t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i d\u7877  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, n\u7871 u v\u7853 y c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7875  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  h\'fat m\'e1u nhi\u7873 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat, sau \u273 \'f3 s\u7869  th\u7917  \u273 \u7873  c\u7853 p \u273 \u7871 n th\u7881 nh c\u7847 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 s\'e1ch l\u432 \u7907 c duy nh\u7845 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  ngh\u297  ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'fac n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t ng\u7901  l\'e0 c\u7917 a r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 m\u7903  ra, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7853 u Grey h\u417 i kinh ng\u7841 c, nh\u432 \u7899 n m\'e0y: "Sao c\u7853 u l\u7841 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean n\u7855 m v\u7841 t \'e1o, kh\u7869  n\'f3i v\u7899 i ti\'ean sinh qu\u7843 n gia: "T\'f4i c\'f3 m\u7897 t s\u7889  vi\u7879 c, mu\u7889 n g\u7863 p Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7913 ?" B\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\u7853 u h\u417 i ch\u7897 t d\u7841 , nh\'ecn Grey t\u7915  d\u432 \u7899 i l\'ean tr\'ean, d\'e1ng v\u7867  th\u259 m d\'f2 v\'e0 th\u7881 nh c\u7847 u d\'e8 d\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 i\u7879 n h\u7841  h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i c\u7917 a." Grey l\u7849 m b\u7849 m, m\u7903  c\u7917 a cho c\u7853 u, "C\u7853 u ng\u7891 i \u7903  ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch ch\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, t\'f4i \u273 i h\u7887 i xem b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  c\'f3 ti\u7879 n g\u7863 p c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 i h\u7887 i hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\'f3 \u273 \'f3i kh\'f4ng, gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u432 a. Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7921  \u273 \u7897 ng phi\'ean d\u7883 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua chi\u7871 c sofa v\u7843 i tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn s\u7841 ch s\u7869  ng\u259 n n\u7855 p l\u7841 i tho\u7843 i m\'e1i trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i, t\u7921  gi\'e1c \u273 \u7913 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean sofa, tay v\u7851 n n\u7855 m v\u7841 t \'e1o nh\u432  c\u361 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n l\'e0m l\u7897 n x\u7897 n \u273 \u7891  d\'f9ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fat h\u417 i ng\u432 \u7901 i trong nh\'e0 c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i. Th\u7921 c t\u7871  c\u7853 u \u273 ang c\'f3 \u7843 o gi\'e1c d\u7841  d\'e0y xo\u7855 n l\u7841 i, \u273 \u7847 u \'f3c tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng, th\u7853 m ch\'ed t\'e2m tr\'ed \u273 ang kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chuy\u7879 n g\'ec l\u7841 i t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7907 i l\'e1t n\u7919 a khi g\u7863 p Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer s\u7869  l\'e0 t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh g\'ec, b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 i ph\u7843 i bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n ra sao m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng tr\u7907  gi\'fap \'97\'97 kh\'f4ng n\'ean hy v\u7885 ng xa v\u7901 i s\u7921  tr\u7907  gi\'fap th\'e2n thi\u7879 n g\'ec g\'ec \u273 \'f3, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n ph\u7843 i tr\u7843  gi\'e1 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, c\'f3 th\u7875  xin \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ra tay l\'e0 t\u7889 t r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng t\'ecm t\u417 \u769 i c\u432 \u777 a c\u7847 u ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ch\'e2n tay lu\u7889 ng cu\u7889 ng, hu\u7889 ng chi c\'e1i vi\u803  c\u7853 u s\u7903  c\u7847 u kia c\'f2n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\'ednh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\'e1t sau Grey t\u7915  l\u7847 u hai xu\u7889 ng, l\'e0m \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c th\u7911  th\u7871  m\u7901 i c\u7853 u l\'ean l\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7845 p th\u7887 m theo Grey l\'ean l\u7847 u, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f2n c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng h\u417 n so v\u7899 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean b\u7883  mang \u273 \u7871 n cho Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey mang theo c\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'e1nh c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng quen thu\u7897 c, ch\u7881  ch\u7881  chi\u7871 c kh\u259 n l\u7909 a m\'e0u \u273 en treo tr\'ean tay n\u7855 m c\u7917 a: "Quy c\u7911  c\u361 , c\u7853 u hi\u7875 u ch\u7913 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7847 m kh\u259 n l\u7909 a b\u7883 t k\'edn m\u7855 t, \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nhi\uc0\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  cao h\u417 n nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, \'e1nh s\'e1ng c\u361 ng m\u417 \u768  h\u417 n, to\'e0n b\u7897  kh\'f4ng gian ph\u7911  k\'edn m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i kh\'ed t\u7913 c \u273 \u7863 c th\'f9 m\'e0 quen thu\u7897 c r\u7845 t nh\u7841 t, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7895 i l\u7847 n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \'f4m c\u7853 u h\'fat m\'e1u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\u7871 t, n\u417 i n\'e0y l\'e0 kh\'f4ng gian ri\'eang ho\'e0n to\'e0n ch\u7881  thu\u7897 c v\u7873  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng kh\'e9p l\u7841 i, ng\u417  ng\'e1c \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  huy\u7873 n quan, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i qu\'ean c\u7843  c\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n khi m\u7897 t thanh \'e2m l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o vang l\'ean trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u, "L\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y" .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 thanh \'e2m c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7899 i h\u7891 i th\u7847 n l\u7841 i, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u417 i gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 o ti\u7871 n l\'ean ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, cho \u273 \u7871 n khi hai tay ch\u7841 m v\'e0o c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843  kinh, \u273 \u7913 ng nguy\'ean t\u7841 i ch\u7895 , v\'f4 th\u7913 c mu\u7889 n thu tay l\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nhanh h\u417 n c\u7853 u, \u273 \'e3 m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c c\u7847 m hai c\'e1nh tay c\u7853 u k\'e9o \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\u7915 a r\u7891 i ph\u7887 ng \u273 o\'e1n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 ang ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gh\u7871  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c c\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng, l\u7841 i nghe th\u7845 y qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u th\u7843 n nhi\'ean n\'f3i: "Ng\u7891 i l\'ean."\cb1 \
