\cb3 "H\uc0\u7843 ? !" Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p h\'e0m ngh\u297 a c\u7911 a c\'e2u n\'e0y, h\u417 i h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng \u273 \u7913 ng t\u7841 i ch\u7895 , Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n kh\'f4ng ki\'ean nh\u7851 n, kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c tr\'f4ng ch\u7901  c\u7853 u ngoan ngo\'e3n t\u7921  m\'ecnh ng\u7891 i l\'ean n\u7919 a, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \u432 a tay d\'f9ng l\u7921 c \'f4m c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh, th\u7843  xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u dang ch\'e2n ng\u7891 i tr\'ean \u273 \'f9i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i n\'f3ng l\'ean, nh\u432 ng r\u7845 t nhanh c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u nguy\'ean nh\'e2n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\'e0m v\u7853 y, h\u417 i th\u7903  l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o kia \u273 ang phun tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u, c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 v\u7883  tr\'ed c\'f3 g\'f3c \u273 \u7897  t\u7889 t ti\u7879 n cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng h\u417 i n\'e2ng c\u7893  v\u7873  ph\'eda sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u417  th\u7875  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u nghi\'eang v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, d\'f9ng r\u259 ng nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng vu\u7889 t ve ph\u7847 n c\u7893  tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i b\u7845 t an, c\u7853 u kh\u7869  nh\'fac nh\'edch, sau khi do d\u7921  m\u7897 t l\'e1t nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... M\u7901 i ng\'e0i d\'f9ng b\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c m\'ecnh c\'f3 n\'ean n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y hay kh\'f4ng. X\'e9t cho c\'f9ng, nh\u7919 ng m\'f3n l\u7849 u hay c\'e1 n\u432 \u7899 ng c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng \u259 n kh\'f4ng d\u7841 y c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \u7875  th\u7921 c kh\'e1ch th\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7913 c m\'ecnh. Sau khi n\'f3i xong c\u7853 u h\u417 i h\u7889 i h\u7853 n, nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y nghe v\'e0o tai th\u7853 t ngu.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, r\u259 ng nanh \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u l\u7841 i d\'e0i ra m\u7897 t ch\'fat, tay tr\'e1i c\'e1ch \'e1o s\u417 mi l\u432 \u7899 t qua l\u432 ng c\u7853 u t\u7915  tr\'ean xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i: "... H\'f4m nay sao l\u7841 i ngoan nh\u432  v\u7853 y? Ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng mu\u7889 n ta \u259 n ng\u432 \u417 i. C\u7889  \'fd t\u7899 i t\'ecm ta l\'e0 c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i run kh\u7869  \u273 \u7897 ng, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t, ch\'ednh m\'ecnh \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\'f3 m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch ri\'eang kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'f4ng th\u7875  g\u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c con qu\u7927  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u g\u7847 n nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u417 n \u273 au v\'e0 h\'e0n \'fd tr\'ean chi\u7871 c r\u259 ng s\u7855 c nh\u7885 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng nh\u7899  t\u7899 i kho\'e1i c\u7843 m m\u7895 i l\u7847 n b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c mang t\u7899 i cho m\'ecnh. C\u417  th\u7875  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  m\'e0 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7869  run.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n nh\uc0\u7899  r\'f5 s\'e1ch l\u432 \u7907 c l\'fac \u273 \u7871 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Cho n\'ean c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, ch\u7881  h\u417 i n\'e2ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean, l\u7841 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u432 a c\u7893  l\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c. C\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u259 ng nanh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e2m th\u7911 ng da, m\'e1u men theo r\u259 ng nh\u7885 n ch\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\'e2u g\'ec \u273 \'f3, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nghe r\'f5. C\u7853 u ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t l\'e0 v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 b\u7887  qua s\u7921  hi\u7871 u k\u7923  v\'e0 tinh th\u7847 n t\'ecm hi\u7875 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7851 n n\u7841 i tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \'e2m r\u259 ng nanh v\'e0o, c\u7921 c nhanh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 bu\'f4ng hai c\'e1nh tay c\u7853 u ra, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i \'f4m s\'e1t l\u432 ng c\u7853 u giam c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'e2ng hai c\'e1nh tay \u273 ang bu\'f4ng th\'f5ng hai b\'ean, m\'ea ly \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7893  con qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y r\u7845 t l\'e2u hai ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7899 i t\'e1ch ra, Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 m ch\'ed ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t v\'ec m\'e1u m\'ecnh ch\u7855 c s\u7855 p b\u7883  h\'fat kh\'f4 lu\'f4n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Emmer c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng tay \u273 ang \'f4m c\u7853 u m\'e0 gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  hai l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, m\u7897 t tay \'f4m eo m\u7897 t tay \'f4m g\'e1y, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n c\u7853 u, d\u7909  d\u7895  c\u7853 u h\'e9 mi\u7879 ng, \u273 \u432 a n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t sang. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngoan ngo\'e3n nu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t d\u7883 ch th\u7875  c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'f3 l\u7907 i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c h\u7891 i ph\u7909 c c\u417  th\u7875 , m\'e0 hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u c\u226 \u768 n c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh mau ch\'f3ng h\u7891 i ph\u7909 c \u273 \u7875  \u7913 ng ph\'f3 v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n ti\u7871 p theo.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng gi\'e3y gi\uc0\u7909 a, mu\u7889 n tr\'e1nh kh\u7887 i \'f4m \u226 \u769 p c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7913 ng xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer l\u7841 i \u273 \'e8 c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  n\'f3i: "Hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i cho ta bi\u7871 t, \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm ta r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 v\'ec chuy\u7879 n g\'ec r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "Kh\'f4ng l\u7869  ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u273 \u417 n thu\u7847 n mu\u7889 n ta h\'fat m\'e1u ng\u432 \u417 i? H\u7843 ? Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i nghe ra t\'e2m t\'ecnh Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\u7879 . Hy v\u7885 ng sau khi h\u7855 n u\u7889 ng no m\'e1u s\u7869  th\u7853 t s\u7921  d\u7877  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng qu\'ean m\u7845 t gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a, th\'e0nh th\'e0nh th\u7853 t th\u7853 t duy tr\'ec v\u7883  tr\'ed, t\u7853 n l\u7921 c bu\'f4ng th\u7845 p t\u432  th\'e1i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, l\'f2ng \u273 \u7847 y kh\u7849 n c\u7847 u: "L\'e0 c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n mu\u7889 n xin ng\'e0i gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , t\'f4i mu\u7889 n xin ng\'e0i gi\'fap t\'f4i c\u7913 u m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u d\'f9ng ng\'f3n c\'e1i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng vu\u7889 t ve g\'e1y c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec th\'eam.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng th\u7845 p th\u7887 m b\u7845 t an ch\u7901 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\'ean ti\u7871 ng th\'fac gi\u7909 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau m\uc0\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\u7899 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng, gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n v\u7851 n b\'ecnh th\u7843 n nh\u432  c\u361 , t\u7915  ng\u7919  kh\'ed c\u7911 a h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng nghe ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4ng tin h\u7919 u d\u7909 ng g\'ec. H\u7855 n ch\u7853 m r\'e3i n\'f3i: "Ta ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  ra tay gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7875 m n\'e0y l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 nghe th\u7845 y trong chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a Emily.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7847 u xin ng\'e0i." C\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'ed c\'f4ng v\'f4 l\u7921 c th\u7881 nh c\u7847 u, "T\'f4i s\u7861 n l\'f2ng trao \u273 \u7893 i c\'f9ng ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 c\'e1ch duy nh\u7845 t c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i coi tr\u7885 ng \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh v\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n. C\u7853 u \u273 \u7883 nh *tay kh\'f4ng b\u7855 t s\'f3i tr\u7855 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o, mu\u7889 n d\u7921 a v\'e0o t\'ecnh c\u7843 m ho\u7863 c khu\'f4n m\u7863 t \u273 \u7875  m\u432 u c\u7847 u ch\u7881  s\u7907  c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. C\'f3 l\u7869  bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p duy nh\u7845 t ch\u7881  c\'f3 c\'f9ng h\u7855 n \u273 \u7841 t th\'e0nh \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n trao \u273 \u7893 i nh\u432  l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, tuy r\u7857 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh c\'f3 g\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e2m.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (tay kh\'f4ng b\uc0\u7855 t s\'f3i tr\u7855 ng : th\'e0nh ng\u7919  mang ngh\u297 a x\u7845 u, \'fd n\'f3i kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 \u273 i kh\u7855 p n\u417 i d\'f9ng th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n l\u7915 a g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 "A?" H\uc0\u7855 n nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\u7887 i, "Ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng gi\'e1 \u273 \u7875  trao \u273 \u7893 i v\u7899 i ta?" T\u7921 a h\u7891  c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  l\u7901 i th\u7881 nh c\u7847 u c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'ed d\uc0\u7909  nh\u432 ..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i, "V\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c khi t\'f4i r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Sophus, ng\'e0i v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\'fat m\'e1u t\'f4i. Nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u qu\'e1 ho\u7843 ng l\u7841 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \'e3 \u273 em to\'e0n b\u7897  th\u7867  \u273 \'e1nh b\u7841 c v\'e0 \'e1t ch\u7911  b\'e0i b\'e0y ra cho \u273 \u7889 i th\u7911 . C\u7853 u qu\u7843  th\u7921 c l\'e0 \u273 ang n\'f3i r\'f5 r\'e0ng cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng bi\u7871 t, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n ng\'e0i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n c\u7911 a t\'f4i, ng\'e0i mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec t\'f4i c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7873  ngh\u7883  kh\'f4ng t\u7879 ." Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u7847 m ng\'e2m m\u7897 t l\'e1t, m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i, trong thanh \'e2m nhi\u7873 u th\'eam v\'e0i ph\u7847 n h\u7913 ng th\'fa, "Nh\u432 ng ta c\'f2n mu\u7889 n c\'e1i kh\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7873 m th\u7913 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng l\'ean, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t nh\u7887  y\u7871 u b\u7883  k\u7867  s\u259 n m\u7891 i \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t \u273 \u7871 n, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1nh m\u7855 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u th\'e2m tr\u7847 m r\u417 i tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh, suy ngh\u297  vi\u7879 c g\'ec \u273 \'f3. M\'e0 c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7897 t m\u7921 c kh\'f3a l\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng, h\u417 i ng\u7891 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i l\'fang t\'fang nh\u7899  t\u7899 i v\u7883  tr\'ed x\u7845 u h\u7893  l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u m\'edm m\'f4i d\u432 \u7899 i, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "Xin m\u7901 i ng\'e0i n\'f3i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c nghi\'eang th\'e2n k\u7873  s\'e1t v\'e0o c\u7853 u, thanh \'e2m tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p, mang theo v\'e0i ph\u7847 n \'fd v\u7883  kh\'e1c vang l\'ean b\'ean tai:\cb1 \
\cb3 "Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i l\u432 u l\u7841 i, b\u7891 i ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0... \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n \u273 \u7875  ta ra tay."\cb1 \
