\cf2 \cb3 Y\uc0\u7871 t h\u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1i, trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u cho l\'e0 m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u sai. C\u7853 u m\u7903  to hai m\u7855 t, mu\u7889 n xuy\'ean qua l\u7899 p kh\u259 n l\u7909 a \u273 en ch\u7855 n \'e1nh s\'e1ng r\u7845 t t\u7889 t kia nh\'ecn th\u7845 u \'fd \u273 \u7891  th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 ph\'ed c\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\'e0i c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  \u273 \'f4\u777 i \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng?" C\u7853 u th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 h\u7887 i, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'f4i h\u417 i kh\'f4, theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng du\u7895 i l\u432 \u7905 i kh\u7869  li\u7871 m li\u7871 m m\'f4i d\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, ch\u7881  \u432 u nh\'e3 m\'e0 th\u7901  \u417  g\'f5 l\'ean th\'e0nh gh\u7871  g\u7895  ch\u7855 c d\'e0y b\'f3ng lo\'e1ng, ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 nh\'e8 nh\u7865  m\'e0 n\u7863 ng n\u7873  c\'f3 ti\u7871 t t\u7845 u quanh qu\u7849 n trong c\u259 n ph\'f2ng y\'ean t\u297 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u, l\u7897  ra ph\u7847 n g\'e1y tr\u417 n b\'f3ng, c\u7853 u d\'f9ng thanh \'e2m g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y n\'f3i: "T\'f4i hi\u7875 u r\u7891 i. T\'f4i... \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 \u432 a tay \'f4m c\u7853 u xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i, t\u7915  ph\'eda sau \'f4m eo c\u7853 u, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u d\'f9ng r\u259 ng nanh \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o trong g\'e1y c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7875  h\'e0m r\u259 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ho\'e0n to\'e0n g\u259 m v\'e0o trong ph\u7847 n da v\u7915 a r\u7891 i b\u7883  ng\'f3n c\'e1i vu\u7889 t ve \u273 \u7871 n h\u417 i n\'f3ng l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u432  th\u7871  h\'fat m\'e1u khi\u7871 n l\u7891 ng ng\u7921 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\'ednh s\'e1t v\'e0o l\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ho\'e0n to\'e0n nh\u7889 t ch\u7863 t l\u7841 i chi\u7871 m l\u7845 y. Con qu\u7927  kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\'e0i th\u7887 a m\'e3n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi r\'fat r\uc0\u259 ng ra, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c v\u7915 a li\u7871 m mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng v\u7915 a c\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng th\u7847 m th\'ec: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u417 i cho r\u7857 ng ta mu\u7889 n l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n g\'ec kh\'f4ng hay v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u417 i ch\u7913 ? Ta ch\u7881  l\'e0... mu\u7889 n \'f4m ng\u432 \u417 i t\u7853 n t\'ecnh u\u7889 ng m\'e1u m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \u7887  l\'ean. V\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'edch x\'e1c \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u l\u7847 m, song n\u7871 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 b\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer h\'fat m\'e1u m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam th\'ec c\'f3 v\u7867  v\u7851 n d\u7877  ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c than th\u7903  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, \'f4m c\u7853 u c\'e0ng s\'e1t th\'eam, \'e2m s\u7855 c tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p: "Ng\u432 \u417 i c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i c\u7917 a, ta c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mu\u7889 n \u259 n ng\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang \u273 \u7845 y, t\'f4i \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'edch x\'e1c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7891 i l\u7849 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean im l\u7863 ng ngh\u297 , ngay sau \u273 \'f3 ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n c\u7845 p b\'e1ch nh\u7845 t hi\u7879 n gi\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i ch\u7919 a trong b\u7843 y hai ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean m\u7899 i m\u7899 i hi\u7879 u qu\u7843 , \u273 \u7875  ch\u7853 m s\u7907  s\u7869  sinh bi\u7871 n, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f2n s\u7869  c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  kh\'e1c ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t tr\u432 \u7899 c, v\u7851 n l\'e0 n\'ean c\u7847 u Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer nhanh ch\'f3ng ra tay c\u7913 u Giang \u272 i\u7873 n m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7883 nh quay m\u7863 t sang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, nh\u432 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer v\u7851 n \u273 ang kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng g\u259 \u803 m c\u7855 n m\'fat v\'e0o ph\u7847 n da sau c\u7893  c\u7853 u, khi\u7871 n cho \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean v\'f4 c\'f9ng kh\'f3 kh\u259 n. C\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  th\u432 \u417 ng l\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: "T\'f4i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n c\u7911 a ng\'e0i, nh\u432 ng xin ng\'e0i gi\'fap t\'f4i c\u7913 u b\u7841 n c\u7911 a t\'f4i tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng, t\'f4i s\u7869  tr\u7903  l\u7841 i... b\u7891 i ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7847 n c\u7893  \u273 au nh\'f3i, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c than nh\u7865  ra ti\u7871 ng, ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng k\'eau \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n, hai tay v\'f4 l\u7921 c b\u7855 t l\u7845 y c\'e1nh tay Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 ang \'f4m b\'ean h\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u259 ng nanh Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  b\'e1o tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 l\u7847 n th\u7913  ba h\'f4m nay, xem ra ch\'ednh m\'ecnh ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng t\u7899 i c\u7917 a x\'e1c th\u7921 c \u273 \'e3 k\'edch th\'edch h\u7855 n th\'e8m \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c sau khi \u259 n xong l\u7847 n n\u7919 a th\u7887 a m\'e3n li\u7871 m li\u7871 m r\u259 ng nanh, ch\u7901  r\u259 ng nanh l\u7841 i thu v\u7873  m\u7899 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\'e0i l\'f2ng m\'e0 ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "C\'f3 th\u7875 , ta s\u7869  \u273 \u7875  Grey \u273 i c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u417 i. H\u7855 n s\u7869  bi\u7871 t c\u7913 u b\u7841 n ng\u432 \u417 i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7873 u, sau khi x\'e1c nh\u7853 n b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 \'e3 chuy\u7875 n bi\u7871 n t\u7889 t ng\u432 \u417 i s\u7869  ph\u7843 i c\'f9ng Grey quay v\u7873  \u273 \'e2y, ho\'e0n th\'e0nh \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7911 a ch\'fang ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u7883  ngh\u7883 , c\u7853 u th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, sau khi \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c cho ph\'e9p li\u7873 n r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 \u7907 i \u7903  ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng, \u273 \u7907 i c\u7853 u \u273 i ra xong li\u7873 n d\u7851 n c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u m\u7897 t ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng s\'f4 pha, mang cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t ly c\'e0 ph\'ea, m\u7897 t khay b\'e1nh quy socola, m\u7897 t c\u7889 c s\u7919 a chua d\'e2u t\'e2y, m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n salad c\'e1 h\u7891 i hun kh\'f3i, hai l\'e1t b\'e1nh m\'ec n\u432 \u7899 ng v\'e0 m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n th\u7883 t c\u7915 u n\u432 \u7899 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891 , \u273 \'fang m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901  tr\u432 a, \u273 \'e2y coi nh\u432  l\'e0 l\'e0m b\u7919 a tr\u432 a cho c\u7853 u?\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 \u432 a c\u417 m cho c\u7853 u xong li\u7873 n l\'ean l\u7847 u hai, \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  \u273 ang l\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e1c ng\u7891 i d\u7921 a tr\'ean chi\u7871 c gh\u7871  l\u7899 n, c\'fac \'e1o s\u417 mi m\u7903  m\u7897 t n\'fat tr\'ean l\u7891 ng ng\u7921 c, qu\u7847 n \'e1o nh\u259 n nh\'fam, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c n\u7855 m t\'fam. H\u7855 n li\u7871 m li\u7871 m r\u259 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng d\u432  v\u7883 . M\'e0 d\'f9 hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i qu\u7847 n \'e1o x\u7889 c x\u7871 ch c\u7917  ch\u7881  l\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e1c, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n v\u7851 n hi\u7879 n l\'ean kh\'ed ch\u7845 t qu\'fd t\u7897 c t\'f4n qu\'fd c\'f9ng kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  khinh th\u432 \u7901 ng thu\u7897 c v\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p cao.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Xem ra v\uc0\u7915 a r\u7891 i Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  r\u7845 t h\'e0i l\'f2ng m\'e0 tho\u7843  m\'e3n. Trong l\'f2ng Grey y\'ean l\u7863 ng suy \u273 o\'e1n, cung k\'ednh l\'e0m l\u7877  v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng \uc0\u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i \u273 \'e3 \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u7871  ti\u7871 p \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  s\u7869  giao nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  g\'ec cho m\'ecnh, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  li\'ean quan t\u7899 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u. Qu\u7843 n gia \u432 u t\'fa n\'ean gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \'f4ng, lu\'f4n lu\'f4n bi\u7871 t ch\u7911  nh\'e2n m\'e0 m\'ecnh h\u7847 u h\u7841  s\u7869  ra nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  l\'fac n\'e0o, h\u417 n n\u7919 a lu\'f4n s\u7899 m \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7897 i dung nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  l\'e0 g\'ec, Grey t\u7921  ki\'eau m\'e0 ngh\u297 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7915 a \u259 n th\u7883 t c\u7915 u n\u432 \u7899 ng xong, ti\'ean sinh qu\u7843 n gia li\u7873 n \u273 i ra t\u7915  trong ph\'f2ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, l\'f2ng \u273 \u7847 y ch\u7901  mong nh\'ecn \'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u khom ng\u432 \u7901 i: "Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean ng\'e0i c\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c d\'f9ng b\u7919 a, ch\'fang ta c\'f3 \u273 \u7911  th\u7901 i gian \u273 \u7875  \u273 i c\u7913 u b\u7841 n ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n." Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i xong l\u7841 i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng d\'f9ng t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  nhanh nh\u7845 t nh\'e9t hai l\'e1t b\'e1nh m\'ec m\'e0u v\'e0ng v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, "T\'f4i \u273 \'e3 \u259 n no r\u7891 i, ch\'fang ta \u273 i th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey nh\'ecn l\uc0\u432 \u7899 t qua nh\u7919 ng m\'f3n \u259 n kh\'e1c tr\'ean b\'e0n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\u7843 i d\u7863 n nh\'e0 b\u7871 p chu\u7849 n b\u7883  m\u7897 t b\'e0n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i phong ph\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia l\'e1i xe c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7843 o l\'e3o Cao c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n kh\'e1c \u273 i \u259 n c\u417 m, sau \u273 \'f3 kh\'f3a c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng b\u7879 nh l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey nh\'ecn nh\'ecn Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n n\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 ang m\'ea man d\u432 \u7899 i t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a thu\u7889 c, l\u7841 i li\u7871 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, b\'ecnh th\u7843 n n\'f3i: "Ng\'e0i c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n nh\'ecn."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng: "T\'ecnh c\u7843 nh s\u7869  r\u7845 t \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "V\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng n\'f3i xong m\'f3c ra t\uc0\u7915  trong t\'fai \'e1o m\u7897 t b\'ecnh thu\u7889 c nh\u7887 , \u273 \u7893  ra m\u7897 t vi\'ean bao h\'ecnh con nh\u7897 ng, \u273 \'fat v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n. Qua n\u7917 a ph\'fat, \'f4ng l\u7841 i \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean ph\u7843 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, d\'f9ng m\u7897 t h\u7897 p s\u7855 t \u273 \u7879 m d\u432 \u7899 i c\u7893  tay ph\u7843 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, l\u7845 y ra m\u7897 t con dao b\u7857 ng ba\u803 c c\u7855 t c\u7893  tay h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f2ng m\'e1u \uc0\u273 en n\u7891 ng \u273 \u7863 c d\u7847 n d\u7847 n ch\u7843 y ra t\u7915  mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i ch\u7843 y v\'e0o trong h\u7897 p s\u7855 t, gi\'e3y d\u7909 a tr\u432 \u7901 n b\'f2 nh\u432  c\'f3 sinh m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac m\'e1u \u273 en ch\u7843 y h\u7871 t, m\'e1u ch\u7843 y ra bi\u7871 n tr\u7903  l\u7841 i th\'e0nh m\'e0u \u273 o\u777 , Grey m\u7899 i d\'ednh n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh gi\'fap Giang \u272 i\u7873 n b\'f4i l\'ean mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, ch\u7901  h\u7855 n t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec n\u7919 a, n\u7871 u c\u7853 u tin t\u432 \u7903 ng t\'f4i th\'ec hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\'f3 th\u7875  theo t\'f4i \u273 i, ho\u7863 c c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u7903  \u273 \'e2y ch\u7901  ki\u7875 m tra k\u7871 t qu\u7843 . Nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  giao cho t\'f4i l\'e0 mang c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua b\uc0\u7841 n m\'ecnh tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n n\'f3i: "Ch\'fang ta ki\u7875 m tra k\u7871 t qu\u7843  xong r\u7891 i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t nhanh hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e3o Cao c\u361 ng c\u417 m n\u432 \u7899 c xong xu\'f4i tr\u7903  v\u7873 , b\u7885 n h\u7885  lo l\u7855 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u432 a \u259 n c\u417 m, mua hamburger v\u7873  cho c\u7853 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i c\'e1m \u417 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7915  ch\u7889 i, nh\u7853 n hamburger r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 \u259 n xong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey nh\'ecn trong m\uc0\u7855 t ghi trong l\'f2ng, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i n\'e0y v\u7915 a r\u7891 i \u7903  ch\u7895  \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  qu\u7843  nhi\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \u259 n no, n\u7871 u b\u7883  \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  bi\u7871 t ch\u7881  s\u7907  \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  s\u7869  t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i qu\u7843  nhi\'ean ph\u7843 i d\u7863 n d\'f2 nh\'e0 b\u7871 p l\'e0m cho c\u7853 u nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7891  \u259 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n t\u7847 m hai gi\u7901  Giang \u272 i\u7873 n t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u \'f3c h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 minh m\u7851 n, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t h\u7891 ng h\'e0o, nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  c\u417  th\u7875  c\u361 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  g\'ec v\u7873  t\u7845 t c\u7843  h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'eam qua sau khi h\'f4n m\'ea. L\'e3o Cao kh\'e9o l\'e9o n\'f3i cho h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t sau khi h\'f4n m\'ea h\u7855 n h\u432  h\u432  th\u7921 c th\u7921 c m\u7845 t tr\'ed.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey ch\uc0\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng gi\'fap g\u7885 i nh\'e2n vi\'ean y t\u7871  ki\u7875 m tra cho Giang \u272 i\u7873 n l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  ki\u7875 m tra m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c theo d\'f5i th\'eam m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng x\u7843 y ra th\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  xu\u7845 t vi\u7879 n. Tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p l\'e0 b\'e1c s\u297  v\'e0 h\u7897  s\u297  ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch Giang \u272 i\u7873 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch kh\'e1m ch\u7919 a cho Emily, b\u7885 n h\u7885  khen ng\u7907 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n kh\u7887 i r\u7845 t nhanh, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i quy r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 nh\u7901  t\u7889  ch\u7845 t c\u417  th\u7875  Giang \u272 i\u7873 n r\u7845 t t\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey kh\'f4ng th\'fac gi\uc0\u7909 c, ch\u7881  im l\u7863 ng d\'f9ng \'e1nh m\u7855 t n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t n\'ean \u273 i r\u7891 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7865  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, n\'f3i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng v\u7899 i b\u7841 n m\'ecnh xong li\u7873 n m\u432 \u7907 n c\u7899  c\'f9ng Grey r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 ng\u7843  v\u7873  t\'e2y, Th\'e1i D\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh nh\u432  gi\u7919 a tr\u432 a, \'e1nh m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i m\'e0u v\'e0ng c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean y\u7871 u \u273 i, c\'f3 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ti\'eau \u273 i\u7873 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i n\'ean l\u7901 i, nh\u432  \u273 ang th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7843 m ban ng\'e0y m\u7845 t \u273 i, th\u7901 i gian x\'f3i m\'f2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 \'fang l\'e0 gi\u7901  cao \u273 i\u7875 m bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i, xe tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n th\'f4ng tho\'e1ng kh\'f4ng tr\u7903  ng\u7841 i, \'f4 t\'f4 m\'e0u \u273 en lao nhanh tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7903  Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7873  t\u7899 i t\'f2a trang vi\'ean quen thu\u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i theo Grey v\'e0o c\u7893 ng l\u7899 n, ng\u7891 i tr\'ean s\'f4 pha ch\u7901  Grey tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean l\'ean l\u7847 u b\'e1o c\'e1o t\'ecnh h\'ecnh v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7845 y ph\'fat sau Grey tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, cung k\'ednh khom ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "M\u7901 i ng\'e0i l\'ean l\u7847 u, Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  \u273 \'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  b\u7919 a t\u7889 i \u273 ang \u273 \u7907 i ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, quen \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 \u273 i l\'ean l\u7847 u, d\u7921 a theo l\u7879  c\u361  c\u7847 m kh\u259 n l\u7909 a m\'e0u \u273 en bu\u7897 c k\'edn m\u7855 t r\u7891 i m\u7899 i \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi v\'e0o c\uc0\u7917 a c\u7853 u li\u7873 n ng\u7917 i th\u7845 y m\'f9i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n th\u417 m, c\'f2n c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng nh\u7841 c ch\u7853 m r\'e3i \'eam \'e1i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i bao ph\u7911  kh\'f4ng gian y\'ean t\u297 nh. Trong ph\'f2ng r\u7845 t \u7845 m, \u7845 m h\u417 n ph\'f2ng k\'ed t\'fac c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer im l\u7863 ng k\'e9o c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n, nh\u432  l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c ki\'ean nh\u7851 n \u273 \'fat c\u7853 u \u259 n h\u7871 t b\u7919 a t\u7889 i, sau \u273 \'f3 gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'fac s\'e1ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u7863 t c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i m\u7863 t \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u. L\u7847 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c r\u7845 t nh\u7865  r\u7845 t ch\u7853 m, thay v\'ec n\'f3i l\'e0 \u259 n th\'ec n\'ean n\'f3i l\'e0 ch\u7881  \u273 ang \u273 \u417 n thu\u7847 n h\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7909  qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 To\'e0n b\uc0\u7897  qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh r\u7845 t y\'ean t\u297 nh, b\u7885 n h\u7885  g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng ng\'f4n ng\u7919  trao \u273 \u7893 i v\u7899 i nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi k\uc0\u7871 t th\'fac m\u7897 t l\u7847 n h\'fat m\'e1u, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng c\u7853 u ra m\'e0 v\u7851 n duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871 , d\'f9ng m\u7897 t tay \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng l\u7853 t qua l\u7853 t l\u7841 i trang s\'e1ch, c\u7853 u \u273 o\'e1n v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  n\'e0y \u273 ang \u273 \u7885 c s\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  qua m\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7841 i \u273 \u7863 t r\u259 ng l\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u vu\u7889 t ve m\u7897 t l\'fac, c\'f3 \u273 \'f4i khi ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u273 \u417 n thu\u7847 n ma s\'e1t, c\'f3 \u273 \'f4i khi l\u7841 i \u273 \'e2m r\u259 ng nanh v\'e0o, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i h\'fat m\'e1u trong ch\u7889 c l\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\uc0\u7875  kh\'f4ng th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer x\'e1c th\u7921 c r\u7845 t bi\u234 \u769 t h\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7909 , c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'ean xem s\'e1ch, m\u7897 t b\'ean nh\'e2m nhi \u273 \u7891  \u259 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'e0 m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n r\u7845 t th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  th\u7871  qua kho\u7843 ng hai ti\u7871 ng, trong l\'fac \u273 \'f3 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ti\u7871 p n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t cho c\u7853 u hai l\u7847 n. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c bu\'f4ng c\u7853 u ra, d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t ch\u7895  \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u \u273 i v\'e0o t\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  ch\u7881  kh\u259 n l\u7909 a che tr\'ean m\u7855 t m\'ecnh, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u7847 m ng\'e2m m\u7897 t l\'e1t, n\'f3i: "Sau khi \u273 i v\'e0o ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f3 th\u7875  th\'e1o xu\u7889 ng, nh\u432 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c khi \u273 i ra nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i bu\u7897 c l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t h\u7907 p l\'fd. Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n an b\'e0i n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng t\uc0\u7855 m \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m chu\u7849 n b\u7883  m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o s\u417  mi tr\u7855 ng tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn h\u417 i r\u7897 ng, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7853 p g\u7885 n g\'e0ng \u273 \u7863 t c\u7841 nh m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c kh\u259 n l\'f4ng kh\'f4, Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7855 m xong suy \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 qu\u7847 n \'e1o chu\u7849 n b\u7883  cho m\'ecnh thay, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec ch\u7895  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7915 a \'e1o ng\u7911  ho\u7863 c \'e1o t\u7855 m? C\u7853 u th\u7917  m\u7863 c l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7863 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u h\u417 i r\u7897 ng, tay \'e1o v\'e0 v\u7841 t \'e1o \u273 \u7873 u h\u417 i d\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 qu\uc0\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7853 u v\u7889 n c\u7903 i ra \u273 \u7863 t ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean do d\uc0\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\'e2ng gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i v\u7899 i ra ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m: "T\'f4i mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, sao t\'f4i kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a t\'f4i \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ta mang \uc0\u273 i gi\u7863 t s\u7841 ch r\u7891 i, s\'e1ng mai s\u7869  tr\u7843  l\u7841 i." Qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u t\u7921  nhi\'ean \u273 \'e1p, "Ta cho ng\u432 \u417 i m\u432 \u7907 n \u273 \u7891  c\u7911 a ta, \u273 \u7875  ch\u7895  kh\u259 n l\'f4ng, ng\u432 \u417 i h\u7859 n l\'e0 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9ng \uc0\u273 \u7891  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh cho ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c m\u432 \u7907 n, v\u7873  ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n n\'e0y v\u7883  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia h\'ecnh nh\u432  h\u417 i nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh th\'e1i qu\'e1, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n nh\u7899  r\'f5 \'e1o kho\'e1c ngo\'e0i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  v\u7851 n \u273 ang treo trong t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u7903  ph\'f2ng k\'ed t\'fac c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 qu\u7847 n..." C\u7853 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c tao nh\'e3 m\'e0 l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m truy\u7873 n v\'e0o: "Ta cho r\u7857 ng y ph\u7909 c c\u7911 a ta \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7911  d\'e0i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t. Tuy r\u7857 ng cho t\u7899 i gi\u7901  c\u7853 u ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng t\u7853 n m\u7855 t th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\u7841 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, nh\u432 ng c\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o kinh nghi\u7879 m ti\u7871 p x\'fac, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng \'f4m m\'ecnh, v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng kia h\u7859 n l\'e0 r\u7845 t cao. Ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n l\'e0 cao h\u417 n m\'ecnh, c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch l\u7855 m so v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn nh\'ecn m\'ecnh trong g\u432 \u417 ng sau khi m\u7863 c \'e1o, b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  bu\u7897 c kh\u259 n l\u7909 a l\'ean l\u7841 i. Th\u7853 t ra \'e1o s\u417 mi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911  d\'e0i \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 , c\u7853 u v\u7851 n cao h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat so v\u7899 i v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia ngh\u297 , nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u361 ng kh\'ed v\'ec m\u7897 t b\u7897  y ph\u7909 c m\'e0 tranh lu\u7853 n v\u7899 i m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'ecnh \uc0\u273 \'fang l\'e0 \u273 \u7891  v\'f4 d\u7909 ng l\u7841 i nhu nh\u432 \u7907 c, chung quy lu\'f4n l\'e0m x\u7845 u m\u7863 t \u273 \u7891 ng b\'e0o nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \u432 u t\'fa, nh\u432 ng c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  trong truy\u7879 n hay phim si\'eau anh h\'f9ng, nh\'e2n v\u7853 t ch\'ednh m\u7899 i d\'e1m d\u361 ng c\u7843 m \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i k\u7867  \u273 \u7883 ch kh\'e1c lo\'e0i m\u7841 nh h\u417 n m\'ecnh g\u7845 p m\u7845 y l\u7847 n m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ch\'fat s\u7907  h\'e3i. C\u7853 u t\u7921  tr\'e1ch l\u7841 i t\u7921  an \u7911 i m\'ecnh, cam ch\u7883 u s\u7889  ph\u7853 n \u273 i ra kh\u7887 i ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u sau khi th\u7845 y c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \'e1p c\u7853 u ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng h\'fat m\'e1u r\u7845 t l\'e2u, l\u7841 i \u273 \'fat n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t cho c\u7853 u, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7849 y c\u7853 u sang m\u7897 t b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 ang n\u7857 m b\'ean kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y thanh \'e2m tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng: "Ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i \u273 i. S\'e1ng mai ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f3 th\u7875  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh n\'e0y coi nh\u432  \u273 \u7841 t th\'e0nh."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  \u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 i qua c\u7853 u tr\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng trong vi\u7879 n m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng ng\u7911 , l\u7841 i lu\'f4n lo l\u7855 ng cho Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7903  ph\'e0o m\u7897 t h\u417 i. V\u7843  l\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng ng\u7911  tr\'ean chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y, cho n\'ean nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u \u273 \'e3 ti\u7871 n v\'e0o m\u7897 ng \u273 \u7865 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng an, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t qua bao l\'e2u, c\u7853 u d\u7847 n thanh t\u7881 nh trong m\u417 , m\u7903  m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
