\cb3 Mu\uc0\u7889 n v\'e0o trong gi\u7845 c m\u417  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, d\'f9 c\'f3 l\'e0 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
