\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7855 p ch\u259 n v\'e0o," L\'fac n\'e0y thanh \'e2m l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7841 i truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n, "Ng\u432 \u417 i b\u7883  b\u7879 nh, b\'e1c s\u297  n\'f3i do ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911  g\'e2y ra, b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u226 \u768 n t\u297 nh d\u432 \u7905 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7919 ng s\u7901 , v\'f4 th\u7913 c ngoan ngo\'e3n nh\u7845 c ch\u259 n \u273 \u7855 p l\u7841 i. To\'e0n th\'e2n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer kh\'f4ng c\'f3 sinh kh\'ed, t\u7915  n\'e3y \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 ang an v\u7883  b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh c\'e1ch \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng xa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c ch\u7853 m l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat: "Ng\u432 \u417 i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i cho t\u7889 t, ta \u273 \'e3 k\'eau nh\'e0 b\u7871 p chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7891  \u259 n thanh \u273 a\u803 m cho ng\u432 \u417 i, c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 xin ngh\u7881  \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng cho ng\u432 \u417 i. Ch\u7901  ng\u432 \u417 i d\u432 \u7905 ng b\u7879 nh kh\u7887 e l\u7841 i ta s\u7869  \u273 \u7875  Grey \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u417 i v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u h\u417 i \u7843 o n\'e3o, \u273 \'eam qua l\'fac t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  s\u7889 t nh\u7865 , \'fd th\u7913 c c\u361 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i m\u417  h\u7891 , \u273 \'e1ng l\u7869  l\'fac \u7845 y h\u7855 n n\'ean nh\'ecn ra, sau \u273 \'f3 ph\u7843 i ch\u259 m s\'f3c c\u7853 u ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i. Nh\u432 ng ai \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n h\u7855 n b\u7883  m\'ea mu\u7897 i, l\'fac ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau v\u7915 a m\u7873 m v\u7915 a nhi\u7879 t d\u7921 a t\u7899 i, h\u7855 n t\u7921 a nh\u432  tr\'fang t\'e0 c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ch\u7889 ng c\u7921  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\u7855 c ch\u7871 , m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7913 c l\u7921 c kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911  ng\u7911  m\u7845 t trong ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng sau khi t\u7881 nh t\'e1o l\u7841 i m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c m\u7901 i b\'e1c s\u297  \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7849 n b\u7879 nh, nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u7871 t lu\u7853 n l\'e0 v\u7845 t v\u7843  qu\'e1 \u273 \u7897 , c\u7847 n ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7883 ch th\u7875  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7907  gi\'fap ngo\u7841 i th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nhanh ch\'f3ng kh\u7887 i, c\u417  th\'e2n th\u7875  kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c nhanh h\u417 n, x\'fac ti\u7871 n h\u7879  th\u7889 ng t\u7841 o m\'e1u, tr\'e1nh cho m\u7845 t m\'e1u qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ch\u7919 a kh\u7887 i b\'e1ch b\u7879 nh. Tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i t\'ecm b\'e1c s\u297 , n\'ean ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i, n\'ean ti\u7871 t ch\u7871  v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i ti\u7871 t ch\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, kh\u7869  \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng. \u272 \u7889 i v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n m\'ecnh sinh b\u7879 nh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean, t\u7915  bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7871 n s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n s\u7889 ng trong lo s\u7907 , h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c l\u7841 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng ch\u7907 p m\u7855 t, th\u7875  l\u7921 c v\'e0 tinh l\u7921 c \u273 \u7873 u ti\'eau hao tr\'ean di\u7879 n r\u7897 ng, c\u417  th\u7875  qu\u7843  th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng g\'e1nh v\'e1c n\u7893 i. Ng\u432 \u7901 i ta n\'f3i gi\u7845 c m\u417  ph\u7843 n \'e1nh s\u7921  th\u7853 t, c\'f2n c\'f3 \'fd ki\u7871 n cho r\u7857 ng c\u7843 nh trong m\u417  s\u7869  th\u7875  hi\u7879 n t\'ecnh h\'ecnh c\u417  th\u7875  trong hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c, \u7903  trong hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c m\'ecnh m\u7879 t kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, ch\u7859 ng tr\'e1ch \u273 \'eam qua trong m\u417  c\u361 ng m\u7879 t m\u7887 i th\'e0nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i k\u7923  qu\'e1i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi\'eang nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u quay v\u7873  ph\'eda Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng: "Ng\'e0i gi\'fap t\'f4i xin ngh\u7881  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o?" Sau khi t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u tr\'ecnh t\u7921  th\u7911  t\u7909 c c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng quen l\u7855 m, n\u7871 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 i h\u7885 c bu\u7893 i di\u7877 n thuy\u7871 t th\'ec c\u7853 u s\u7869  b\'f9ng lu\'f4n, b\u7903 i m\u7845 y l\u7899 p c\u7853 u ch\u7885 n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\u7899 p b\u7855 t bu\u7897 c; n\u7871 u l\'e0 bu\u7893 i h\u7885 c nh\u7887  th\'ec s\u7869  g\u7917 i th\u432  xin ngh\u7881  cho th\u7847 y ho\u7863 c tr\u7907  gi\u7843 ng. Cho n\'ean c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng r\'f5 v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  n\'e0y d\'f9ng th\'e2n ph\u7853 n g\'ec l\'fd do n\'e0o \u273 \u7875  xin ngh\u7881  cho m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer r\u7845 t t\'f9y \'fd m\'e0 \u273 \'e1p: "Tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c v\'e0 h\u7879  th\u7889 ng gi\'e1o d\u7909 c \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng c\'f3 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. N\'f3i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, s\u7869  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i thu x\u7871 p, vi\u7879 c n\'e0y ng\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n lo l\u7855 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\'e1 to mi\uc0\u7879 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec. C\u7853 u l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c n\'e0y \u7849 n n\'fap trong x\'e3 h\u7897 i lo\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7871 n bao nhi\'eau, c\'f3 l\u7869  b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f2n n\u7855 m gi\u7919  quy\u7873 n l\u7921 c x\'e3 h\u7897 i m\u7841 nh h\u417 n so v\u7899 i c\u7853 u t\u432 \u7903 ng. Xin ngh\u7881  th\u7853 t s\u7921  ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c nh\u7887  ch\u7859 ng \u273 \'e1ng \u273 \u7875  n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c nh\'ecn c\u7853 u h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng c\'f2n t\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7853 u kh\'e1t n\u432 \u7899 c, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u432 ng m\u7897 t b\'e1t canh b\'ed \u273 \u7887  t\u7899 i, n\'e2ng c\u7853 u d\u7853 y d\'f9ng th\'eca \u273 \'fat t\u7915 ng mu\u7895 ng cho c\u7853 u: "Kh\'e1t sao? Mu\u7889 n \u259 n g\'ec kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 n\'f3ng kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean x\'e1c th\uc0\u7921 c c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\u7915 a kh\'e1t v\u7915 a \u273 \'f3i b\u7909 ng, li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i, y\'ean l\u7863 ng u\u7889 ng t\u7915 ng h\'fap canh nh\u7887 . C\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c h\'f4m nay Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer l\u7841 i k\u7923  qu\'e1i h\u417 n, k\u7923  qu\'e1i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c\'97\'97 th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \'e3i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n qu\u7843  th\u7921 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \'f4ng ch\u7891 ng \u273 ang h\u7847 u h\u7841  b\'e0 x\'e3 mang thai. Ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\'e0 x\'e3 \'e0 em kh\u7893  c\u7921 c r\u7891 i ph\u7843 i \u259 n nhi\u7873 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i nhi\u7873 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3ng gi\u7853 n...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u h\u417 i s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t, nhanh ch\'f3ng \'e9p \'fd ngh\u297  qu\u7927  d\u7883  trong \u273 \u7847 u n\'e0y xu\u7889 ng. C\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 b\u7883  s\u7889 t \u273 \u7871 n h\u7891  \u273 \u7891  r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4m c\uc0\u7853 u h\'fat m\'e1u nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n nh\u432  th\u7871 , th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u kh\'e1 h\u417 n c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Nh\u432  c\u7853 u th\'edch l\u7849 u, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c h\u7887 i th\'edch \u259 n g\'ec nh\u7845 t c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u n\'f3i l\'e0 l\u7849 u. N\u7871 u l\'e0 c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\u7891 i l\u7849 u tr\u7903  th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  \u273 \u7889 i x\u7917  v\u7899 i n\'f3 c\'f2n t\u7889 t h\u417 n so v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \u7889 i x\u7917  v\u7899 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean l\'fac Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c h\u7887 i mu\u7889 n \u259 n g\'ec, Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i \u259 n l\u7849 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c hai gi\'e2y: "Kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ch\u7901  ng\u432 \u417 i kh\u7887 i b\u7879 nh r\u7891 i n\'f3i sau. Ta cho ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i n\u7845 u ch\'e1o cho ng\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng, thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "V\u7853 y t\'f4i mu\u7889 n \u259 n ch\'e1o tr\u7913 ng mu\u7889 i th\u7883 t n\u7841 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, ph\u7911  k\'edn ch\u259 n cho c\u7853 u xong \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u7903  trong khung c\u7843 nh y\'ean t\u297 nh d\u7847 n thi\u7871 p \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f2a trang vi\'ean n\'e0y l\'e0 Grey mua t\uc0\u7841 m th\u7901 i, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'fang gi\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n qu\'e9t d\u7885 n, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \u7847 u b\u7871 p b\u7903 i n\u417 i n\'e0y c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai c\u226 \u768 n \u259 n c\u417 m. M\u7895 i l\u7847 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7899 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i t\u7841 m th\u7901 i thu\'ea tr\u7885 n nh\'e2n vi\'ean b\u7871 p c\u7911 a nh\'e0 h\'e0ng ph\u7909  c\u7853 n. M\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0m ch\'e1o tr\u7913 ng mu\u7889 i th\u7883 t n\u7841 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng: "T\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i m\u7901 i \u273 \u7847 u b\u7871 p nh\'e0 h\'e0ng Trung Hoa t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n." Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kho\'e1t tay \'e1o, "Ta c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  l\'e0m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey do d\uc0\u7921  m\'e0 nh\'ecn Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  c\u7911 a \'f4ng, tuy r\u7857 ng \'f4ng bi\u7871 t r\'f5 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y lu\'f4n l\'e0 s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i nh\u7845 t trong th\u7871  gi\u7899 i h\u7855 c \'e1m, nh\u432 ng \'f4ng kh\'f4ng cho l\'e0 ch\u7911  nh\'e2n xu\u7845 t s\u7855 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  xu\u7845 t s\u7855 c trong m\u7845 y vi\u7879 c nh\'e0 b\u7871 p n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean v\uc0\u7883  qu\u7843 n gia ti\'ean sinh n\'f3i m\u7897 t \u273 \u7857 ng l\'e0m m\u7897 t n\u7867 o n\u7885  li\u7873 n m\u7901 i m\u7897 t v\u7883  \u273 \u7847 u b\u7871 p m\'f3n Trung v\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7897 i nh\'e2n vi\'ean v\u7879  sinh t\'f9y th\u7901 i ch\u7901  l\u7879 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 \'f4ng sai r\u7891 i, sau khi nguy\'ean li\u7879 u v\'e0 d\u7909 ng c\u7909  nh\'e0 b\u7871 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7871 n, r\u7845 t nhanh Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \'e3 d\'f9ng khay b\u432 ng m\u7897 t b\'e1t g\u7889 m c\u7905  v\u7915 a v\'e0 m\u7897 t b\'e1t g\u7889 m c\u7905  nh\u7887  \u273 i ra, m\'f9i c\u417 m th\u417 m t\u7915  trong b\'e1t g\u7889 m lan ra, l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta h\u7847 u nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'f9i v\u7883  n\'f3ng h\u7893 i th\u417 m d\u7867 o kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer d\'f9ng th\u7921 c l\u7921 c ch\u7913 ng minh v\u7899 i \'f4ng, c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'f3 th\u7875  v\'f4 c\'f9ng xu\u7845 t s\u7855 c \u7903  m\u7885 i ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7881 nh d\u7853 y li\u7873 n \u259 n ch\'e1o n\'f3ng trong b\'e1t, c\u417 m m\u7873 m th\u417 m h\u432 \u417 ng tan trong mi\u7879 ng, m\u7863 n nh\u7841 t v\u7915 a v\u7863 n, v\'e0o b\u7909 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1i c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u7845 m l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\'f9ng th\'eca \u273 \'fat cho c\u7853 u, b\'ecnh th\u7843 n m\'e0 nh\u432  v\'f4 t\'ecnh m\'e0 h\u7887 i: "Ngon kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\'fat keo ki\uc0\u7879 t khen ng\u7907 i: "Ngon, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 b\'e1t ch\'e1o ngon nh\u7845 t t\'f4i t\u7915 ng \u259 n t\u7915  khi \u273 \u7871 n Sophus." N\'f3i th\u7853 t ra th\'ec, l\'fac \u7903  trong n\u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u259 n ch\'e1o ngon l\'e0nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y. M\u7865  kh\'f4ng gi\u7887 i n\u7845 u c\u417 m, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n n\u7845 u ch\'e1o cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  n\u7845 u th\'e0nh \u273 \u7863 c d\'ednh s\u7873 n s\u7879 t g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n n\u432 \u7899 c d\u432 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\uc0\u7889 t." Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer vui m\u7915 ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, "\u258 n ch\u7853 m th\'f4i, c\'f3 m\u7897 t n\u7891 i, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i, ta kh\'f4ng cho ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u259 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u7903  ch\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ba ng\'e0y m\u7899 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y k\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u7921 c k\u7923  th\'edch \'fd, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y th\'ec m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u t\u7889 t. C\'f3 \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i mi\u7879 ng, gi\u432 \u7901 ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i d\u7877  ch\u7883 u, c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh ph\'e1t thanh \u273 \u7863 c s\u7855 c, th\u7853 m ch\'ed th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer c\'f3 h\u7913 ng s\u7869  \u273 \'edch th\'e2n \u273 \'e0n piano cho c\u7853 u nghe.\cb1 \
