\cb3 M\'e0 trong th\uc0\u7901 i gian n\'e0y Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 \u273 ang chi\u7871 u c\u7889  c\u7853 u hay ch\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  l\'e0 nguy\'ean t\u7855 c gi\u7919  g\'ecn s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e kh\'f4ng \u259 n \u273 \u7891  \u259 n c\'f3 b\u7879 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai \uc0\u273 \'eam sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam c\u7853 u ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c \u273 \u7871 n s\'e1ng, kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  m\u417 ; m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam l\u7841 i m\u417  th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n l\'e0 khung c\u7843 nh gi\u7889 ng l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, gian ph\'f2ng r\u7897 ng r\'e3i, gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n m\u7873 m m\u7841 i, \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0u cam \u7845 m \'e1p, nam nh\'e2n m\u7863 c s\u417  mi tr\u7855 ng ng\u244 \u768 i d\u432 \u803 a tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0u \u273 en tr\u7847 m, \u273 \'f4i ch\'e2n thon d\'e0i \u273 \u7875  t\u7921  nhi\'ean tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c l\u7859 ng l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, n\'e9t m\u7863 t r\u7845 t nhu h\'f2a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u432  nh\u7919 ng gi\u7845 c m\u417  tr\u432 \u7899 c d\u7921 a s\'e1t t\u7899 i \'f4m h\u7855 n, c\u7903 i n\'fat \'e1o s\u417  mi c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t n\u7917 a l\u7841 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u h\u7841  n\u7909  h\'f4n l\'ean c\u7893  h\u7855 n, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y nh\'e9t k\u7929  c\u7853 u v\u7873  trong ch\u259 n, l\'f4ng m\'e0y kh\u7869  \u273 \u7897 ng, bi\u7875 u l\u7897  mu\'f4n ph\u7847 n b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297 , d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang c\u7889  h\u7871 t s\u7913 c kh\u7855 c ch\u7871 : "Em b\u7883  b\u7879 nh, kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng m\u7899 i kh\u7887 e l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m b\u7853 y, n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 c k\u7879  c\u7853 u b\'e1n manh th\u7871  n\'e0o \u259 n v\u7841  th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, d\'f9 \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t x\u7845 u h\u7893  m\'e0 c\u7889  \'fd m\u7873 m nh\u361 n gi\u7885 ng c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i\u7879 u g\u7885 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 l\'e3o c\'f4ng, nam nh\'e2n v\u7851 n b\u7845 t vi s\u7903  \u273 \u7897 ng, nhi\u7873 u nh\u7845 t c\u361 ng ch\u7881  \u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng c\'e1ch ch\u259 n \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, \'e2m \u273 i\u7879 u l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m d\u7895 : "L\'e3o c\'f4ng \'f4m em ng\u7911 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 ang \u7903  trong m\u7897 ng l\u7841 i b\u7883  \'f4m ng\u7911 , h\'f4m sau t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y \u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t (*)th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng, kinh ho\u7843 ng gi\u7899 i h\u7841 n trong gi\u7845 c m\u417  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng th\u7845 p, l\u7841 i c\u7843 m kh\'e1i c\'e1c c\u7909  n\'f3i c\u7845 m c\'f3 sai, qu\u7843  nhi\'ean l\'e0 ng\'e0y c\'f3 ngh\u297  \u273 \'eam c\'f3 m\u7897 ng, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh b\u7883  b\u7879 nh ph\u7843 i mau kh\u7887 e, ngay c\u7843  n\u7897 i dung gi\u7845 c m\u417  c\u361 ng gi\'fap c\u7843 n m\'ecnh ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c l\'e0m b\u7853 y l\u259 n qua l\u259 n l\u7841 i b\u7915 a b\'e3i trong m\u7897 ng.\cb1 \

