\f1 , trong truy\uc0\u7879 n h\'ecnh nh\u432  t\u7915 ng n\'f3i y\'eau qu\'e1i s\u7869  th\'f4ng qua c\'e1ch nh\u7853 p m\u7897 ng m\'e0 h\u7845 p th\u7909  tinh kh\'ed ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\'f3 l\u7869  d\'f9 ch\u7881  l\'e0 n\u7857 m m\u417 , m\'ecnh v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m nh\u7919 ng gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng kia c\u361 ng \u273 \'fang l\'e0 hao t\u7893 n tinh l\u7921 c v\'e0 th\u7875  l\u7921 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'e2m th\u7847 m h\u7841  quy\u7871 t t\'e2m, ng\'e0y mai s\u7869  ph\u7843 i l\u7845 y cu\u7889 n "Gi\'e1 tr\u7883  quan c\u7889 t l\'f5i c\u7911 a ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a x\'e3 h\u7897 i" ra h\u7885 c thu\u7897 c m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c hoang d\'e2m sa \u273 \u7885 a \u273 i xu\u7889 ng trong x\'e3 h\u7897 i t\u432  b\u7843 n ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\'e0y n\'e0y \uc0\u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng lu\'f4n im l\u7863 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n cho c\u7853 u, ch\u7881  c\'f3 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u g\u7885 i cho c\u7853 u h\u7887 i th\u259 m t\'ecnh h\'ecnh: "Th\u432 \u7899 c k\u7867 , sao c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng quay v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1? T\'f4i \u273 i h\u7887 i qu\u7843 n l\'fd, b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\u7843 o c\u7853 u b\u7883  b\u7879 nh, b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 ang \u7903  nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n, ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u xin ngh\u7881  cho c\u7853 u. C\u7853 u c\'f3 h\u7885  h\'e0ng \u7903  Sophus \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i n\'f3i d\u7889 i: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i h\u7885  h\'e0ng, l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n c\u7911 a cha t\'f4i \u273 ang c\'f4ng t\'e1c \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, m\u7901 i t\'f4i \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 b\'e1c \u7845 y \u259 n c\u417 m. K\u7871 t qu\u7843  \u273 \'fang h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i b\u7883  b\u7879 nh, b\'e1c \u7845 y li\u7873 n gi\u7919  t\'f4i l\u7841 i d\u432 \u7905 ng b\u7879 nh, t\'f4i s\u7855 p v\u7873  r\u7891 i." \u272 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i trong l\'f2ng suy ngh\u297  ni\'ean k\u7881  c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 o\'e1n ch\u7915 ng l\'e0m b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a \'f4ng c\u7889  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\u361 ng c\'f2n mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng, ch\u7855 c ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'ednh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng th\u7901 i k\u7923  v\u7899 i l\'e3o t\u7893  t\'f4ng \u273 \'e3 h\'f3a th\'e0nh tro nh\'e0 m\'ecnh m\'e0 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n kh\'f4ng h\u7873  nghi ng\u7901  ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n l\u7901 i gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c Grey \u273 \u432 a v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 li\u7873 n gi\u7903  xem th\u432  v\'e0 b\u432 u ph\u7849 m m\'e0 m\'ecnh b\u7887  qua m\u7845 y ng\'e0y v\u7915 a r\u7891 i, \u273 \u7841 i \u273 a s\u7889  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 th\'f4ng b\'e1o v\u7873  ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a k\'fd t\'fac v\'e0 tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t ch\'fa \'fd. Ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh h\u7885 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\u361 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, ngh\u7881  h\u7885 c ba ng\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'f3 b\'f9. Sau khi xem qua m\u7897 t l\u7847 n l\u7853 t c\u7853 u \'e1ng ch\u7915 ng trong b\u7909 ng, th\'f4ng tin duy nh\u7845 t \u273 \'e1ng ch\'fa \'fd ch\'ednh l\'e0 ba ng\'e0y sau tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c s\u7869  cho ngh\u7881  h\u7885 c m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i, hai tu\u7847 n kh\'f4ng l\'ean l\u7899 p, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  c\u7853 u nh\'e2n d\u7883 p l\'fac n\'e0y th\u7901 i ti\u7871 t m\u7885 i n\u417 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7841 nh l\u7855 m, \u273 i nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i kh\'e1c \u7903  \'dac ch\u417 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7885 c k\u7923  tr\u432 \u7899 c Giang \u272 i\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 i m\u7897 t l\u432 \u7907 t nh\u7919 ng th\'e0nh ph\u7889  v\'e0 khu phong c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i n\u7893 i danh, v\'ec kh\u7843  n\u259 ng t\'e0i ch\'ednh c\'f3 h\u7841 n v\'e0 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  s\u7855 p x\u7871 p th\u7901 i gian n\'ean kh\'f4ng t\'ednh \u273 i th\'eam l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n n\'f3i c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\'fap Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\'ean h\u7879  b\u7841 n \u273 \u7891 ng h\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 ang nh\u7855 n tin v\u7899 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t tin nh\u7855 n, l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7917 i t\u7899 i, h\u7887 i c\u7853 u m\u7845 y ng\'e0y v\u7915 a r\u7891 i th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\'e0y kh\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7899  li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, m\'ecnh v\u7915 a t\u7915  ch\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer tr\u7903  v\u7873  h\u7855 n li\u7873 n g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n, t\'ean n\'e0y ch\u7885 n th\u7901 i gian c\u361 ng tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p th\u7853 t \u273 \u7845 y. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nhanh ch\'f3ng g\'f5 ch\u7919 , k\u7875  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n m\u7845 y ng\'e0y v\u7915 a r\u7891 i, c\u361 ng h\u7887 i h\u7855 n sao l\u7841 i tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\u7843 i th\'edch hai ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c h\u7855 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n theo d\'f5i m\u7897 t t\'ean qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'f3 h\'e0nh vi tr\'e1i lu\u7853 t \u273 \u7875  \u273 i\u7873 u tra ch\u7913 ng c\u7913 , cho n\'ean b\u7853 n r\u7897 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  thuy\u7871 t ph\u7909 c. C\u7853 u vi\u7871 t: "Anh ch\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, em g\u7885 i cho anh."\cb1 \
\cb3 Y\'ean t\uc0\u297 nh, im \u7855 ng, trong ph\'f2ng t\u7889 i t\u259 m nh\u432  ph\u7847 n m\u7897 , qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh tr\'ean chi\u7871 c gh\u7871  g\u7895  l\u7899 n. T\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng \u7845 m \'e1p, \'e2m nh\u7841 c, h\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c \u259 n th\u417 m v\'e0 \'e2m thanh kho\'e1i ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t theo nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i duy nh\u7845 t t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7863 t ch\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 khung c\u7843 nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \'e3 quen, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t quen thu\u7897 c v\u7899 i c\'e1c qu\'fd t\u7897 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 s\u7889 ng l\'e2u t\u7915  th\u7901 i c\u7893  x\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7859 ng l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t s\'e1ng l\'ean, ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng chu\'f4ng d\u7877  nghe.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u273 \u7875  kh\'f3e m\'f4i kh\'f4ng nh\u7871 ch l\'ean r\'f5 r\'e0ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \'e1p l\'ean tai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thanh \'e2m c\'f2n d\u7877  nghe h\u417 n, th\'f4ng qua s\'f3ng \u273 i\u7879 n, v\u7915 a nh\u7865  v\u7915 a m\u7873 m, r\u417 i th\u7859 ng v\'e0o trong l\'f2ng h\u7855 n: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, d\u7841 o n\'e0y anh c\'f3 r\u7843 nh kh\'f4ng... Em mu\u7889 n g\u7863 p anh m\u7897 t l\u7847 n. \u7914 m, h\u7887 i v\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer g\'ec g\'ec \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f3e m\'f4i Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7871 ch l\'ean m\u7897 t \u273 \u7897  cong c\'e0ng l\u7899 n. Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i, h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t m\'e0, t\u7889 i qua n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam sau khi t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y l\u7841 i kh\'f3c \'f4m h\u7855 n ngoan ngo\'e3n k\'eau l\'e3o c\'f4ng, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\'f2n \'f4m ch\u7863 t tay h\u7855 n, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u bu\'f4ng ra, t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  nh\u7899  h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7899  h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n g\u7863 p h\u7855 n c\'f2n mu\u7889 n ki\u7871 m c\u7899 , c\'f2n d\'f9ng h\u7855 n l\'e0m c\u7899 , th\u7853 t l\'e0 x\u7845 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n cong cong m\u7855 t, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn tr\u7901 i sao ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 , nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng \u273 \'e1p: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, v\u7915 a b\'e1o c\'e1o t\'ean qu\u7927  kia xong, c\'f3 th\u7875  ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian, d\u7841 o n\'e0y l\'fac n\'e0o t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian tr\u7889 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m kia r\'f5 b\'ecnh t\uc0\u297 nh l\u7841 i t\u7921  nhi\'ean, l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng nghe ra \u273 i\u7875 m g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7901 .\cb1 \
