 th\u7845 y t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y c\'f2n nh\u7899  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p k\u7875  h\u7871 t cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n b\u7887  d\u7903  gi\u7919 a ch\u7915 ng. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t b\'ean c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u r\u7917 a b\'e1t m\u7897 t b\'ean th\u7847 m kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i, trong n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 vui v\u7867  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  che gi\u7845 u. H\u7855 n d\'f9ng d\u432  quang li\u7871 c qua Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang ch\u259 m ch\'fa k\u7875  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n m\'ecnh \u273 i nh\'e0 tr\u7867 , trong l\'f2ng \u273 \u7855 c \'fd ngh\u297  m\u7895 i ng\'e0y em b\'e0y ra b\u7897  d\u7841 ng \u273 \u7841 o m\u7841 o nghi\'eam trang nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\u7899 i ta, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ta t\'ecnh c\u7901  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\'ec c\'f2n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t em ngh\u297  g\'ec v\u7873  ta trong m\u7897 ng \u273 \'e2u. Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i. H\u7855 n l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ch\u432 a \u273 \u7911 , r\u7845 t mu\u7889 n n\'f3i cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ng\u7841 i, d\'f9 \u7903  trong hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c h\'f4n h\u7855 n \'f4m h\u7855 n s\u7901  h\u7855 n g\u7885 i h\u7855 n l\'e3o c\'f4ng h\u7855 n c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \u7845 y. Hoan ngh\'eanh gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng c\u7911 a em tr\u7903  th\'e0nh s\u7921  th\u7853 t. B\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng d\'f9 c\'e1i t\'ean n\u7857 m m\u417  kia nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec c\'e1i k\u7867  t\'ecnh nh\'e2n trong m\u7897 ng b\u7883  xem nh\u432  \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng n\u7857 m m\u417  l\'e0 h\u7855 n c\u361 ng s\u7855 p kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a r\u7891 i.. Th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 k\u7875  xong, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng r\'f3t cho c\u7853 u m\u