\u7897 ng kh\'e9o \u273 \u432 a ra l\u7901 i \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  g\u7863 p m\u7863 t: "... L\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u n\'f3i mu\u7889 n \u259 n m\u7897 t n\u7891 i l\u7849 u n\u432 \u7899 c d\'f9ng \u273 \u7887  \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? Gi\u7901  t\'f4i \u273 ang mu\u7889 n th\u7917  l\'e0m m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, c\u7853 u c\'f3 mu\u7889 n qua th\u7917  kh\'f4ng?" L\u7901 i \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  v\'f4 c\'f9ng h\u7845 p d\u7851 n. Th\u7871  nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n nh\u7883 n \u273 au c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t: "B\'e2y gi\u7901  em kh\'f4ng v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, em \u273 ang \u7903  Cairns." "\u7902  Cairns?" "V\'e2ng, \u273 i du l\u7883 ch. H\'f4m qua em v\u7915 a \u273 i l\u7863 n \u7903  r\u7863 ng san h\'f4 Great Barrier, h\'f4m nay \u273 i Kuranda, b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 ang tr\'ean t\'e0u h\u7887 a t\u7915  Kuranda tr\u7903  v\u7873  n\u7897 i th\'e0nh Cairns." \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c t\'e0u h\u7887 a ki\u7875 u c\u361  m\'e0 du kh\'e1ch c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7855 m phong c\u7843 nh, ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0 s\u7843 n ph\u7849 m c\u7911 a th\u7871  k\u7927  tr\u432 \u7899 c, t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  r\u7845 t ch\u7853 m, c\u7917 a s\u7893  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  do k\'e9o ra, toa t\'e0u b\u7857 ng g\u7895  m\'e0u v\'e0ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7845 u t\u7841 o b\'e0i tr\'ed c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\u7901 i \u273 \u7841 i tr\'f4i qua, th\u7853 t ra l\u7841 i c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c thi v\u7883  \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t. Trong xe c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ho\'e0n to\'e0n c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  ch\u7885 n ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i. T\'e0u \u273 i xuy\'ean qua r\u7915 ng r\u7853 m ch\u432 a khai th\'e1c, t\'edn hi\u7879 u tr\'ean xe c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, thanh \'e2m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe v\'e0o tai r\u7845 t k\'e9m, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 l\u7855 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  c\u7917 a toa \u273 \u7875  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i r\u7845 t kh\'f3 th\'f4ng qua gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i \u273 \u7875  ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t c\u7843 m x\'fac c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. "... C\u7853 u \u273 i khi n\'e0o?" "Ch\'ednh l\'e0 sau h\'f4m \u259 n l\u7849 u \u7845 y, t\u7915  h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 tr\u432 \u7901 ng em cho ngh\u7881  hai tu\u7847 n." B\'ean kia d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i m\u7897 t gi\'e2y: "M\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u7853 u?" "Kh\'f4ng, em \u273 i v\u7899 i ba b\u7841 n h\u7885 c n\u7919 a, hai n\u7919  m\u7897 t nam. Giang \u272 i\u7873 n gi\'fap em li\'ean h\u7879  \u273 \u7845 y, tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 em c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t. Nh\u432 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  t\u7889 t l\u7855 m, \u273 i ch\u417 i v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  r\u7845 t vui." \u272 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t l\'e0 ba ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n \u273 \u7891 ng h\'e0nh c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m du l\u7883 ch phong ph\'fa, n\u259 ng l\u7921 c t\'ednh to\'e1n v\'e0 th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t m\u7841 nh, s\u7855 p x\u7871 p t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i th\u7913  nhanh g\u7885 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng. Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 em th\'edch ta sao, sao c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng r\u7911  ta m\u7897 t c\'e2u \u273 \'e3 \u273 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c? H\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n gi\u7919  b\'ed m\u7853 t gi\u7887 i \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\'f3i quen \u273 \u259 ng \u7843 nh du l\u7883 ch l\'ean m\u7841 ng, hai ng\'e0y nay l\'fac n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7873  li\'ean quan, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  ra n\'ean ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng n\'f3i cho h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Sophus \u273 i du l\u7883 ch. Em kh\'f4ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng \u273 i ch\u417 i nu\'f4i d\u432 \u7905 ng t\'ecnh c\u7843 m v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 m m\u7871 n, \u273 \u7871 n bao gi\u7901  ch\'fang ta m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  b\'ean nhau trong hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c \u273 \'e2y? C\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\'f2n tr\'f4ng ch\u7901  t\'ecnh nh\'e2n trong m\u7897 ng c\u7911 a em ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng t\u7899 i quy\u7871 n r\u361  em hay kh\'f4ng? Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi bu\u7897 t mi\u7879 ng h\u7887 i: "Sao c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t? \u272 \u7875  t\'f4i \u273 i t\'ecm c\u7853 u." Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7845 t kinh ng\u7841 c: "Em n\'f3i v\u7899 i anh r\u7891 i m\'e0, h\'f4m \u259 n l\u7849 u \u7845 y, anh c\'f2n li\'ean t\u7909 c c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u. Ch\u7855 c l\'e0 anh qu\'ean r\u7891 i. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 anh c\u361 ng \u273 \u7915 ng t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, ph\'f2ng b\u7885 n em \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ph\'f2ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, anh t\u7899 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  \u7903 . H\u417 n n\u7919 a ng\'e0y mai em l\'ean m\'e1y bay \u273 i Sydney r\u7891 i, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i t\u7915  Sydney quay v\u7873  Sophus." Ph\'f2ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i... Em c\'f2n \u7903  c\'f9ng ch\u7895  v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghi\'eam m\u7863 t tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c, l\'fac \u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 ang ng\u7855 m ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i th\u7845 t th\u7847 n t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng nh\u7919 ng c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p, qu\'e1 m\u7913 c \u273 \u7855 c \'fd, th\u7871  n\'ean \u273 \'e3 b\u7887  l\u7905  tin quan tr\u7885 ng nh\u432  th\u7871 . Th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0, ki\'eau binh t\u7845 t b\u7841 i. A Di\'ean hay ng\u7841 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t \'fap \'fap m\u7903  m\u7903  tho\'e1ng nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng r\u7911  m\'ecnh, m\'ecnh v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i b\u7887  l\u7905 . H\u7855 n \u7843 o 