\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915  b\u7887  \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh b\'e1o c\u7843 nh s\'e1t xin gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , y\'ean l\u7863 ng chuy\u7875 n di \u273 \u7897 ng sang ch\u7871  \u273 \u7897  im l\u7863 ng, b\u7845 m s\u7889  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  trong t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng n\'e0y, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean t\'ecm th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u s\u7869  hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  h\u417 n. C\u7853 u h\u417 i h\u7889 i h\u7853 n h\'f4m qua \u273 \'e3 t\u7915  ch\u7889 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm m\'ecnh. B\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'f3 l\u7869  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n \u273 ang \u7903  Sophus, ch\u7881  mong l\'e0 h\u7855 n c\'f3 bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p c\'f3 th\u7875  li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  \u7903  Sydney.\cb1 \
