\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u417  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn di \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh h\'f3a th\'e0nh b\u7897 t m\u7883 n d\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n h\u7855 n, nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t, im l\u7863 ng xu\u7889 ng. Hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n m\u7841 o hi\u7875 m khi\'eau chi\u7871 n hai con qu\u7927  n\'e0y, b\u7903 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 t c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'e1u th\u7883 t x\u432 \u417 ng c\u7889 t m\'ecnh b\u7883  \u273 \u7841 p th\'e0nh b\u7897 t ph\u7845 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y s\u7869  l\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7909 c ng\u7919  n\'f3i Di\'eam V\u432 \u417 ng d\u7877  g\u7863 p ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  kh\'f3 ch\u417 i, t\u7915  c\'e1ch \u273 \u7889 i x\u7917  v\u7899 i B\u7841 ch Thu v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7911 a b\u7885 n ch\'fang c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e2n t\'edch ra \'edt nh\u7845 t b\u7889 n con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 mu\u7889 n h\'fat kh\'f4 m\'e1u m\'e0 l\'e0 mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t ch\u7895 , n\u7871 u th\u7871  c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7853 u s\u7869  g\u7863 p qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u cao c\u7845 p h\u417 n, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean y\'ean l\u7863 ng theo d\'f5i k\u7923  bi\u7871 n, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 l\u7869  s\u7869  c\'e1ch tho\'e1t v\'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f3 ti\u7871 p m\'e1y c\'f3 nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng, nh\u432 ng hy v\u7885 ng \'edt nh\u7845 t h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng nghe m\'e1y, nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'fac g\u7885 i l\u7841 i cho c\u7853 u nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng g\u7885 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, h\u7855 n s\u7869  \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n. H\u7855 n c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u \u273 ang \u7903  Sydney, cho n\'ean h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  ngh\u297  c\'e1ch t\u7899 i c\u7913 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hu\uc0\u7889 ng h\u7891 , b\u7845 t k\u7875  th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 n\'f3i, t\u7889 t x\u7845 u g\'ec c\u7853 u c\u361 ng n\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c coi nh\u432  l\'e0 m\'f3n \u259 n y\'eau th\'edch c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer... \u273 i?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\u7871 u sau n\'e0y t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c nguy\'ean li\u7879 u l\'e0m l\u7849 u \u273 \u7873 u ng\u7915 ng s\u7843 n xu\u7845 t, m\'ecnh nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  n\u7893 i \u273 \'f3a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \u7843 o m\u7897 t v\'f2ng r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \'fd ngh\u297  c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng c\u7913 u c\u7853 u m\u7897 t m\u7841 ng, nh\u7919 ng \'fd ngh\u297  n\'e0y l\'e0m c\u7853 u tho\'e1ng an \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7841 i. Tr\u7843 i qua th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i \u7903  chung v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n b\'ecnh y\'ean v\'f4 s\u7921  khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n qu\'e1 s\u7907  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac B\uc0\u7841 ch Thu tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7853 u h\'ecnh nh\u432  h\u417 i kinh ng\u7841 c, nh\u432 ng mi\u7879 ng b\u7883  nh\'e9t n\'f3i ch\u7859 ng n\'ean l\u7901 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng d\'f9ng \'e1nh m\u7855 t ra hi\u7879 u v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng d\'f9ng m\u7855 t ra hi\u7879 u ch\'e0o h\u7887 i v\u7899 i c\'f4, c\u361 ng hy v\u7885 ng \'edt nhi\u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7845 n an c\'f4 g\'e1i \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0y. Tuy r\u7857 ng hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f4 n\'e0ng l\'e0 th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 ch\u7885 c ph\u7843 i m\u7845 y con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tr\'f4ng th\uc0\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean, B\u7841 ch Thu x\'e1c th\u7921 c an t\'e2m h\u417 n kh\'f4ng \'edt, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c li\u7873 u m\u7841 ng gi\'e3y d\u7909 a n\u7919 a m\'e0 an t\u297 nh l\u7841 i nh\u432  c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai con qu\uc0\u7927  k\'e9o B\u7841 ch Thu \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, \u273 \u7849 y hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i v\'e0o m\u7897 t ga ra ng\u7847 m b\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, xong \u273 \u7849 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\'e0o trong m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c xe. Hai con qu\u7927  ng\u7891 i gh\u7871  l\'e1i v\'e0 gh\u7871  l\'e1i ph\u7909 , hai con kh\'e1c ng\u7891 i c\'f9ng ph\'eda sau tr\'f4ng b\u7885 n h\u7885 , sau khi \u7845 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i xu\u7889 ng gh\u7871  ng\u7891 i li\u7873 n l\u7845 y b\u259 ng d\'ednh \u273 en d\'e1n k\'edn m\u7855 t c\u7843  hai, l\u7841 i d\'f9ng b\u259 ng d\'ednh tr\'f3i tay ch\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m o\'e1n ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  t\u7845 t c\u7843  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7873 u th\'edch b\u7883 t m\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\'f2n tr\'ean l\'e0m d\u432 \u7899 i theo, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 noi theo Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n ch\'fang?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng so s\'e1nh ra th\'ec gi\u7901  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ho\'e0i ni\u7879 m kh\u259 n l\u7909 a \u273 en m\'e0 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer chu\u7849 n b\u7883  m\u7895 i l\u7847 n, \'edt nh\u7845 t kh\u259 n l\u7909 a r\u7845 t m\u7873 m, r\u7845 t nh\u7865 , h\u417 n n\u7919 a th\'f4ng kh\'ed, ch\u7881  l\'e0 ch\u7855 n s\'e1ng t\u7889 t, bu\u7897 c tr\'ean m\u7855 t cho d\'f9 mang l\'e2u c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u. M\'e0 v\u7915 a m\u7899 i b\u7883  l\u7899 p b\u259 ng d\'ednh \u273 en n\'e0y tr\'f3i l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\'e1t c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, m\u7855 t c\u361 ng b\u7883  \u273 \'f3ng ch\u7863 t, m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7903  ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  nh\'e9t trong mi\u7879 ng B\u7841 ch Thu h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7845 y ra, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y c\'f4 g\'e1i ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh h\'e1 l\u7899 n mi\u7879 ng th\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 hai con qu\u7927  kia kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\u7919 a, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n r\u7857 ng hai nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i nh\u7887  y\u7871 u n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 s\u7913 c b\u7887  ch\u7841 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau, hai Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia n\'f3i kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, kh\u7849 u \'e2m r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7845 t m\u7845 t c\'f4ng m\u7899 i ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7897 i dung b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, nghe xong hai c\'e2u th\u7845 y c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 th\'f4ng tin g\'ec c\'f3 \'fd ngh\u297 a c\u361 ng li\u7873 n t\u7915  b\u7887 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \'d4 t\'f4 ch\uc0\u7841 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t l\'fac kh\'e1 l\'e2u th\'ec d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh v\'e0 B\u7841 ch Thu l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7905  b\u259 ng d\'ednh tr\'f3i tay ch\'e2n \u273 \u7849 y xu\u7889 ng xe. B\u7885 n h\u7885  b\u7883  kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \'e9p \u273 i xu\u7889 ng c\u7847 u thang c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u b\u7853 c quanh co, sau khi \u273 i qua m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\u7883  giam v\'e0o m\u7897 t ch\u7895  \'97\'97 c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng kh\'f3a c\u7917 a v\'e0 ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n \u273 i xa.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7889 n ph\'eda an t\u297 nh tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i ch\u7901  trong ch\u7889 c l\'e1t, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac x\'e1c nh\u7853 n xung quanh kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai m\u7899 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng g\u7885 i: "B\u7841 ch Thu, B\u7841 ch Thu?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u7853 u th\u7845 y may m\'e0 nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  kia kh\'f4ng b\u7883 t mi\u7879 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng n\'f3i y\u7871 u \u7899 t c\u7911 a c\'f4 g\'e1i truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n t\u7915  n\u417 i kh\'f4ng xa: "T\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean men theo h\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng \'e2m thanh t\u7915  t\u7915  d\u7883 ch t\u7899 i g\u7847 n, cho \u273 \u7871 n khi c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\u7869  \u273 \u7909 ng v\'e0o c\u417  th\u7875  \u7845 m \'e1p c\u7911 a c\'f4 g\'e1i m\u7899 i lui v\u7873  ph\'eda sau m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i. C\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7853 u n\'ean c\u7843 m \u417 n "Hu\u7845 n luy\u7879 n" c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng trong b\'f3ng \u273 \'eam \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u m\'e0 n\'f3i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 kh\'f3 kh\u259 n g\'ec qu\'e1 l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i th\u259 m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: "C\u7853 u l\'e0 sao m\'e0 b\u7883  m\u7845 y con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia b\u7855 t?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u?" B\u7841 ch Thu gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  gi\u7901  m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t th\'e2n ph\u7853 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng qu\'e1i v\u7853 t kia, trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i l\u7897  ra kinh ng\u7841 c v\'e0 ho\u7843 ng s\u7907  kh\'f3 n\'e9n, "Th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 \u432 ? V\u7853 y ch\'fang ta... s\u7869  ra sao \u273 \'e2y..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean an \uc0\u7911 i: "Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i s\u7907 , b\'ecnh t\u297 nh l\u7841 i, s\u7869  c\'f3 c\'e1ch th\'f4i. Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u n\'f3i cho t\'f4i nghe c\u7853 u l\'e0m sao m\'e0 b\u7883  ch\'fang b\u7855 t?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7841 ch Thu m\u7897 t b\'ean nh\u7899  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t b\'ean nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng \u273 \'e1p: "V\u7915 a r\u7891 i tr\u7901 i m\u432 a, t\'f4i \u273 ang tr\'fa m\u432 a d\u432 \u7899 i hi\'ean m\u7897 t qu\'e1n c\'e0 ph\'ea, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean m\u7897 t nam sinh da tr\u7855 ng r\u7845 t cao \u273 i t\u7899 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i t\'f4i, h\u7855 n r\u7845 t tu\u7845 n t\'fa, \u259 n m\u7863 c c\u361 ng d\u7877  nh\'ecn, t\'f4i r\u7845 t c\'f3 h\u7843 o c\u7843 m v\u7899 i ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7855 n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta gh\'e9t, nh\'ecn qua kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i x\u7845 u, l\u7841 i \u273 \'fang l\'fac tr\u7901 i \u273 ang m\u432 a, t\'f4i ngh\u297  d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7907 i m\u432 a t\u7841 nh, v\u7853 y n\'ean n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i h\u7855 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u trong l\'f2ng, di\u7879 n m\u7841 o \u273 \u7865 p qu\u7843  l\'e0 d\u7877  che gi\u7845 u h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\u7841 i c\'e0ng d\u7877  ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f3 m\'e0 t\u7915  ch\u7889 i, B\u7841 ch Thu n\'f3i r\u7845 t th\'e0nh th\u7853 t, \u273 \'fang l\'e0 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng th\u7853 t c\u7911 a c\'f4. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n l\'e0 Alex, Simon, hay Grey, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 t\u7845 t c\u7843  nam n\u7919  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c t\u7853 n m\u7855 t nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u7903  y\u7871 n h\u7897 i m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3, \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 b\u7873  ngo\'e0i xu\u7845 t s\u7855 c. M\'e0 nh\'ecn l\u7841 i th\u7901 i gian, l\'fac tr\u7901 i m\u432 a h\'ecnh nh\u432  ch\'ednh l\'e0 l\'fac m\'ecnh \u273 i tham quan nh\'e0 th\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7841 ch Thu ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c k\u7875 : "T\'f4i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n trong ch\u7889 c l\'e1t, th\u7845 y m\u432 a d\u7847 n nh\u7887  l\u7841 i li\u7873 n mu\u7889 n c\'e1o bi\u7879 t h\u7855 n. Nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n b\u7895 ng n\'f3i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i h\u7855 n h\u7871 t pin, nh\u7901  t\'f4i d\u7851 n h\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t n\u417 i, t\'f4i h\u417 i l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  ch\u432 a \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, h\u7855 n li\u7873 n l\u7845 y th\u7867  sinh vi\'ean trong v\'ed ra, n\'f3i h\u7855 n l\'e0 sinh vi\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c Sydney, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i x\u7845 u, th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i h\u7871 t pin m\'e0 l\u7841 i h\u7865 n g\u7863 p b\u7841 n \u7903  \u273 \'f3. T\'f4i th\u7845 y h\u7855 n l\u7845 y th\u7867  sinh vi\'ean ra c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nghi ng\u7901  n\u7919 a, h\u417 n n\u7919 a xem tr\'ean b\u7843 n \u273 \u7891  c\u361 ng th\u7845 y n\u417 i \u273 \'f3 g\u7847 n qu\'e1n c\'e0 ph\'ea, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c h\u417 i kh\'f3 t\'ecm, cho n\'ean \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd d\u7851 n h\u7855 n \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7895  \u273 \'f3 r\u7845 t h\u7867 o l\'e1nh m\'e0 tr\u7901 i c\'f2n t\u7889 i, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\u7889  xung quanh \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \'e8n. L\'fac g\u7847 n \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i t\'f4i c\u361 ng h\u417 i h\u7889 i h\u7853 n, sau khi ch\u7881  s\u417  qua h\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 i cho h\u7855 n li\u7873 n mu\u7889 n ch\u7841 y \u273 i, l\'fac \u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n li\u7873 n h\u7887 i t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e2u. C\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t ti\u7871 ng Anh c\u7911 a t\'f4i kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t l\u7855 m \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng, l\'fac \u7845 y kh\'f4ng nghe r\'f5, t\u432 \u7903 ng l\'e0 h\u7855 n l\'e0 h\u7887 i t\'f4i c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\u7845 p kh\'f4ng c\'e1c loa\u803 i, t\'f4i n\'f3ng l\'f2ng mu\u7889 n tho\'e1t th\'e2n li\u7873 n thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i ph\u7843 i. K\u7871 t qu\u7843  t\'f4i v\u7915 a tr\u7843  l\u7901 i xong tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t li\u7873 n nhanh ch\'f3ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n ba ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e2y quanh t\'f4i, sau \u273 \'f3 b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7899 i nam sinh v\u7915 a r\u7891 i t\u7899 i t\'ecm t\'f4i nh\u7901  d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kia \u273 \u7873 u t\u7915  t\u7915  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh b\u7897  d\'e1ng qu\u7927  qu\'e1i c\u7853 u v\u7915 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y kia. T\'f4i s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, mu\u7889 n ch\u7841 y, nh\u432 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  r\u7845 t kh\u7887 e, t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  l\u7841 i r\u7845 t nhanh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7883 ch chuy\u7875 n t\u7913 c th\u7901 i. M\u7897 t m\'ecnh t\'f4i c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\u7889 n tho\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 . Chuy\u7879 n sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y." C\'e0ng n\'f3i v\u7873  sau, gi\u7885 ng c\'f4 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7869  run r\u7849 y, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a b\'ecnh t\u297 nh l\u7841 i t\u7915  trong c\u7843 m gi\'e1c s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean an \uc0\u7911 i c\'f4 hai c\'e2u, gi\u7843 i th\'edch: "B\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7845 p th\u7845 p, l\'fac h\'f3a th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c r\u259 ng nanh d\'e0i ra nh\'ecn s\u7869  t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i kinh khungt, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'e1c v\u7899 i l\'fac ng\u7909 y trang th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i. Qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7845 p c\'e0ng cao th\'ec ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh c\'e0ng gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\u361 ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t. V\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  \u273 \'eam h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 l\'fac c\u7853 u b\u7883  \u273 \'e1m Alex v\'e2y quanh, Alex v\u7899 i Simon c\u7845 p b\u7853 c t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i cao, ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  h\u7847 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 bi\u7871 n h\'f3a l\u7899 n, nh\u432 ng ba con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7845 p th\u7845 p kh\'e1c c\u361 ng bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh lo\u7841 i s\u7855 c m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng xanh r\u259 ng nanh d\'e0i ra n\'e0y. C\u7853 u \u273 o\'e1n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer lo\u7841 i c\u7845 p b\u7853 c \u273 \'f3 m\u7895 i l\u7847 n h\'fat c\u7853 u m\'e1u c\'f3 l\u7869  ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  du\u7895 i r\u259 ng nanh ra, c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng thay \u273 \u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao c\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y?" B\u7841 ch Thu nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "T\'f4i \uc0\u273 i du l\u7883 ch, con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng t\'f4i quay v\u7873  kh\'e1ch s\u7841 n. Kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'fang l\'fac tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7853 u b\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  k\'e9o \u273 i, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  l\'fac t\'ecm tr\u7907  gi\'fap b\u7883  ch\'fang ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f2n l\'e0m li\'ean l\uc0\u7909 y t\u7899 i c\u7853 u n\u7919 a, th\u7853 t s\u7921  xin l\u7895 i." Trong gi\u7885 ng c\'f4 c\'f3 \'e1y n\'e1y, c\'f2n c\'f3 ch\'fat bi th\u432 \u417 ng. C\'f3 l\u7869  r\u7845 t bi quan v\u7873  t\u432 \u417 ng lai c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7902  m\u7897 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7901  b\'ean kia \u273 \u7841 i d\u432 \u417 ng b\u7883  m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 s\u7889 ng b\u7855 t c\'f3c \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t n\u417 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\'ean, th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 ngh\u297  th\u7917  \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y r\u7845 t t\u7891 i t\u7879 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i xem b\u7885 n ch\'fang l\'e0m g\'ec ch\'fang ta?" C\'f4 v\u7851 n nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7887 i, tuy r\u7857 ng bi\u7871 t r\'f5 b\u7841 n m\'ecnh c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng \u273 \u432 a ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1p \'e1n ch\'ednh x\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\'ec h\'fat m\'e1u th\'f4i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7845 n an \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, k\u7923  th\u7853 t ch\'ednh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c chuy\u7879 n l\u7847 n n\'e0y k\u7923  d\u7883  h\u417 n so v\u7899 i h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u417 n thu\u7847 n, n\u7871 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 c\u432 \u7905 ng \'e9p h\'fat m\'e1u, h\'fat m\'e1u xong th\'ec x\'f3a tr\'ed nh\u7899  r\u7891 i th\u7843  b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i m\'e0 n\'f3i, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n t\u7889 n c\'f4ng t\u7889 n s\u7913 c nh\u432  th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7843  l\u7887 ng \u273 i." C\u7853 u th\'ec th\u7847 m, "B\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871  \u273 \'e2u, ch\u7859 ng qua l\'fac b\u7883  \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o h\u417 i \u273 au m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i, sau \u273 \'f3 s\u7869  kh\'e1 h\u417 n, nh\u7883 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\'e0 qua r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7921 c ra \u273 \'fang nh\u432  l\u7901 i c\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer h\'fat m\'e1u k\u7923  th\u7853 t r\u7845 t tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, nh\u432 ng d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y, s\u7869  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \'e3 khu\u7845 t ph\u7909 c con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia, c\u7853 u m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u7889 t kh\'ed, d\u7877  d\'e0ng bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh n\'f4 l\u7879  kho\'e1i c\u7843 m b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u. H\u417 n n\u7919 a v\u7873  \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m b\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 m v\u7899 i B\u7841 ch Thu, d\'f9 sao Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i b\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'e0ng m\u7841 nh c\u7845 p c\'e0ng cao h\'fat m\'e1u kho\'e1i c\u7843 m s\u7869  c\'e0ng m\'e3nh li\u7879 t, b\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p th\u7845 p h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c s\u7869  d\u7877  ch\u7883 u nh\u432  l\'fac Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer h\'fat m\'e1u. L\'fac n\'e0y ng\u432 \u7901 i ta l\'e0 th\u7899 t dao m\'ecnh l\'e0 th\u7883 t c\'e1, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7853 n l\u7921 c tr\u7845 n an b\u7841 n m\'ecnh duy tr\'ec b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, kh\'f4ng n\'ean qu\'e1 s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn t\uc0\u7915  \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y, con ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'edch x\'e1c l\'e0 th\u7913 c \u259 n cao c\u7845 p h\u417 n r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i l\u7849 u hay c\'e1 n\u432 \u7899 ng c\'e1c lo\u7841 i, \'edt nh\u7845 t n\u7891 i l\u7849 u ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng b\u7855 t b\u7867  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u259 n ch\'fang. C\u7853 u t\u7921  gi\u7877 u trong l\'f2ng, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng d\'f9ng c\'e1ch n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  gi\u7843 m b\u7899 t c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... C\uc0\u7853 u t\u7915 ng b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u h\'fat m\'e1u sao?" B\u7841 ch Thu kh\u7869  h\u7887 i, "Kh\'f4ng, \'fd t\'f4i l\'e0 t\'f4i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u7853 u r\u7845 t hi\u7875 u m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'fang, t\'f4i t\u7915 ng b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u. \u7902  Sophus, c\'f3 m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  \u273 \'e3 h\'fat m\'e1u t\'f4i r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7883 nh gi\u7845 u gi\u7871 m, r\u7845 t trung th\u7921 c \u273 \'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sophus c\uc0\u361 ng c\'f3 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u?" B\u7841 ch Thu h\'edt kh\'ed l\u7841 nh, "C\u7853 u t\u7915 ng b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n? V\u7853 y sao c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  c\'e1ch tr\u7889 n \u273 i? Ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng v\u7873  n\u432 \u7899 c c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Trong \uc0\u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u h\u7855 n t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i m\u7841 nh, kh\'f4ng d\u7877  \u273 \u7889 i ph\'f3. H\u417 n n\u7919 a b\u7883  h\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u c\u361 ng l\'e0 trong t\'ecnh th\u7871  b\u7913 c b\'e1ch t\'f4i t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n t\u7841 o th\'e0nh kh\u7871  \u432 \u7899 c v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, c\'f3 th\u7901 i h\u7841 n." L\'fac \u7845 y Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer qu\u7843  th\u7853 t \u273 \'e3 cho c\u7853 u l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n, kh\'f4ng ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh, m\u7897 t m\'ecnh r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i; ho\u7863 c l\'e0 ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh, mang Giang \u272 i\u7873 n c\'f9ng r\u7901 i \u273 i. Tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u l\'e0 b\u7883  \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  \u273 \'ea h\'e8n l\u7915 a \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i \u273 \'f3, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n n\'e0o kh\'e1c, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng giao \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n c\u361 , l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, c\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "... T\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n d\'ednh th\'eam phi\u7873 n to\'e1i, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nh\u7883 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\'e0 s\u7869  qua, cho n\'ean th\'e0nh ra c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7841 ch Thu nghe v\u7853 y s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t, nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u: "Th\'ec ra l\'e0 th\u7871 , n\'f3i th\u7853 t, t\'f4i r\u7845 t b\u7897 i ph\u7909 c c\u7853 u. N\u7871 u l\'e0 t\'f4i g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng \u273 \'f3, c\'f3 l\u7869  s\u7869  th\'e0 c\'e1 ch\u7871 t l\u432 \u7899 i r\'e1ch ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng n\u7893 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f2n c\'f3 m\uc0\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m r\u7845 t quan tr\u7885 ng, trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7849 n \u7849 n minh b\u7841 ch, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i ra \'97\'97m\u7897 t nguy\'ean nh\'e2n r\u7845 t quan tr\u7885 ng khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng, l\'e0 v\'ec b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng gh\'e9t Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, kh\'f4ng gh\'e9t h\u7855 n g\u7847 n g\u361 i, kh\'f4ng gh\'e9t h\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gh\'e9t h\u7855 n li\u7871 m g\'e1y c\u7853 u, \u273 \'fat n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t sang cho c\u7853 u. Tuy r\u7857 ng cho \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, nh\u432 ng b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7853 u b\u7857 ng l\'f2ng ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n h\u7855 n th\'e2n m\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7917  t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng n\u7871 u \u273 \u432 a ra \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh n\'e0y l\'e0 Alex ho\u7863 c m\u7845 y con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u h\'f4m nay b\u7855 t c\'f3c hai ng\u432 \u7901 i... Ch\u7881  v\u7915 a ngh\u297  th\u7917  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 mu\u7889 n \u273 i\'ean r\u7891 i, t\'e2m sinh l\'fd \u273 \u7873 u ch\'e1n gh\'e9t ch\u7889 ng c\u7921 . \u272 \u7841 i kh\'e1i c\u7853 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  m\u7873 m d\u7867 o nh\u432  khi \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u v\'ec sao l\u7841 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, c\'e0ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng suy ngh\u297  nguy\'ean nh\'e2n trong \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n r\u7845 t nh\u7865 , c\u7853 u kh\u7869  \u273 \u7849 y B\u7841 ch Thu m\u7897 t c\'e1i, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u259 n \'fd \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i im l\u7863 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7845 t nhanh ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng m\u7903  kh\'f3a, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7917 a b\u7883  \u273 \u7849 y ra, hai con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u chia ra \u273 i v\u7873  hai ph\'eda hai ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7889 n \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  r\u7901 i \u273 i kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 d\'e0i, c\'f2n \u273 i l\'ean r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u b\u7853 c thang, l\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i xu\u7889 ng m\u7845 y b\u7853 c. Xung quanh kh\'f4ng y\'ean t\u297 nh \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\'e0 c\'f2n tho\'e1ng c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng \u7891 n \'e0o truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n. \'c2m thanh huy\'ean n\'e1o c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng vang l\'ean ngay b\'ean tai, m\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 ang gi\u7919  c\u7853 u c\u361 ng d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'ecnh b\u7883  \u273 \u7849 y l\'ean m\u7897 t \u273 \'e0i cao h\u417 n m\u7863 t b\u7857 ng, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng kh\'f4ng v\u7919 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng n\u7917 a qu\u7923  \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh c\u417  th\u7875 , b\u7889 n ph\'eda \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\u7893  l\'ean ti\u7871 ng hoan h\'f4 \u7847 m \u297 .\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t gi\'e2y sau b\u259 ng d\'ednh \u273 en tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t c\u7853 u r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i x\'e9 \u273 i, hai tay v\u7851 n b\u7883  tr\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean s\'e1ng l\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\'edch \u7913 ng nh\u7855 m ch\u7863 t hai m\u7855 t, \u273 \u7907 i m\u7897 t l\'e1t m\u7899 i nheo m\u7855 t t\u7915  t\u7915  m\u7903  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xu\uc0\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh h\'ecnh b\u7847 u d\u7909 c, b\u7889 n b\u7913 c t\u432 \u7901 ng quanh \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7889 t n\u7871 n, tr\'ean m\'e1i v\'f2m h\'ecnh b\u7847 u d\u7909 c treo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 \'e8n ch\'f9m tr\'f2n ki\u7875 u c\u7893 . Quanh \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng, b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7863 c l\u7877  ph\u7909 c, tr\'ean m\u7863 t l\u7841 i \u273 eo m\u7863 t n\u7841  n\u7917 a m\u7863 t c\u7893  qu\'e1i, h\'ecnh d\u7841 ng ho\u7863 c khoa tr\u432 \u417 ng ho\u7863 c qu\u7927  d\u7883 , \u273 a ph\u7847 n m\u7863 t n\u7841  l\'e0 m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u7847 ng t\u7847 ng l\u7899 p l\u7899 p m\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch. Trong \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh \'e1nh s\'e1ng r\u7845 t t\u7889 i, quang \u7843 nh ch\u7853 p ch\u7901 n, chi\u7871 u m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u l\u7901  m\u7901 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t m\'e0n k\u7883 ch r\u7885 i b\'f3ng qu\'e1i \u273 \u7843 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \'e0i cao h\'ecnh b\u7847 u d\u7909 c, cao h\u417 n b\u7889 n ph\'eda kho\u7843 ng n\u7917 a m\'e9t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang \u7903  tr\'ean \u273 \'e0i n\'e0y. B\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u l\'e0 B\u7841 ch Thu, b\'ean tr\'e1i B\u7841 ch Thu c\'f2n c\'f3 ch\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\'e0u da kh\'e1c nhau nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i, \u432 \u7899 c ch\u7915 ng h\u417 n hai m\u432 \u417 i. B\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7913 ng th\'e0nh m\u7897 t h\'e0ng tr\'ean s\'e2n th\u432 \u7907 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'f9ng d\u432  quang \'e2m th\u7847 m li\u7871 c qua, ch\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean tr\'e1i B\u7841 ch Thu s\u7855 c m\u7863 t \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7901  \u273 \u7851 n, \'e1nh m\u7855 t v\'f4 th\u7847 n, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7885 i th\u7913  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng ch\'fat ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn xu\uc0\u7889 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t. Tr\'ean b\u7873  m\u7863 t \u273 \'e0i c\'f3 kh\u7855 c hoa v\u259 n ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7857 ng c\'f3 sinh m\u7841 ng, nh\u7919 ng \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\'e2n l\'f5m s\'e2u xu\u7889 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, h\'ecnh th\'e0nh nh\u7919 ng \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng r\'e3nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u7871 t n\u7889 i th\'f4ng su\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng c\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'f3 d\u7921  c\u7843 m kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t. Nh\u432  \u273 \u7875  nghi\u7879 m ch\u7913 ng ph\u7887 ng \u273 o\'e1n, c\u7853 u ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i h\'ecnh b\'f3ng ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean ph\u7843 i ph\'eda sau c\u7853 u c\u7847 m trong tay m\u7897 t thanh \u273 \u7891  v\u7853 t d\'e0i nh\u7885 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng nh\'ecn, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u361 i khoan ba c\u7841 nh v\'f4 c\'f9ng s\u7855 c nh\u7885 n\'97\'97 tuy r\u7857 ng t\'ean t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 , nh\u432 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y c\'f9ng v\u7899 i kim t\u7921  th\'e1p ba c\u7841 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7885 c trong m\'f4n to\'e1n th\u7901 i ti\u7875 u h\u7885 c s\u417  trung kh\'e1c nhau m\u7897 t tr\u7901 i m\u7897 t v\u7921 c, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t m\u361 i khoan, \u273 \u7847 u m\u361 i khoan l\'e0 ba r\'e3nh, n\u7871 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 o\'e1n kh\'f4ng sai, thi\u7871 t k\u7871  n\'e0y h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \u7875  d\u7877  l\u7845 y m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ra m\u7897 t th\'e2n m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7841 nh, b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i v\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u. C\u7853 u th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng r\'e9t m\'e0 run, n\u7871 u th\u7853 t nh\u432  c\u7853 u \u273 o\'e1n, v\u7853 y th\'ec c\'f2n \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i ch\u7881  b\u7883  ch\'fang h\'fat m\'e1u. Th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 th\u7875  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  m\u7845 t m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cao h\uc0\u417 n \u273 \'e0i l\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7871  \u273 \'e0n, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u sau l\u432 ng l\'e0 \u273 ao ph\u7911 , m\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885 , \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 t\u7871  ph\u7849 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hi\uc0\u7871 n t\u7871  c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, qu\u7927  d\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 m\uc0\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\u7863 c trang ph\u7909 c th\u7901 i trung c\u7893  c\u7847 u k\u7923  \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e0i, c\'f2n cao gi\u7885 ng h\'e1t m\u7897 t kh\'fac nh\u7841 c. L\'e0n \u273 i\u7879 u qu\u7927  m\u7883  hoa l\u7879 , r\u7891 i l\u7841 i l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\'f3 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \'e2m tr\u7847 m. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 d\'f2ng kh\'ed kh\'f4 l\u7841 nh xuy\'ean th\u7845 u linh h\u7891 n c\u7853 u, g\u7847 n nh\u432  mu\u7889 n l\'e0m linh h\u7891 n c\u7853 u \u273 \'f4ng c\u7913 ng. C\u7853 u nh\u432  ng\u7917 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'f9i v\u7883  t\u7917  vong im \u7855 ng, ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n ng\u7911  say d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7897  \u273 \u7883 a v\u7855 ng l\u7841 nh m\'eanh m\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y ph\uc0\u7847 n g\'e1y c\u7853 u b\u7895 ng \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1i, tho\'e1ng n\u7893 i l\'ean ch\'fat c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'f3ng r\u7921 c t\'ea d\u7841 i. \u272 \'f3 l\'e0 ph\u7847 n da Emmer th\'edch c\u7855 n nh\u7845 t, h\u7855 n lu\'f4n th\'edch \'f4m c\u7853 u t\u7915  ph\'eda sau, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e2m r\u259 ng nanh v\'e0o n\u417 i \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 To\'e0n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\'f9ng m\'ecnh, l\'e9n l\'fat d\'f2 x\'e9t ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean tr\'e1i. Bi\u7875 u t\'ecnh c\u7911 a ch\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \u273 \'e3 c\'e0ng ch\u7871 t l\u7863 ng h\u417 n, ngay c\u7843  s\u7855 c m\u7863 t B\u7841 ch Thu c\u361 ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u tr\u7903  n\'ean tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng v\'f4 th\u7847 n, nh\u432  b\u7883  h\'fat \u273 i linh h\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'fac nh\uc0\u7841 c qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ng\'e2m x\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7915 ng n\u7889 t nh\u7841 c \u273 \u7873 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang g\'f5 chu\'f4ng b\'e1o t\u7917 , b\'e1o hi\u7879 u c\'e1i ch\u7871 t \u273 ang t\u7899 i g\u7847 n. M\u361 i dao ba r\'e3nh tr\'ean tay qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  gi\'f2i trong x\u432 \u417 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 c\'f9ng s\u7907  h\'e3i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c khi m\u361 i ch\'f9y kia xuy\'ean th\u7911 ng c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y ph\'e1t sinh, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n ch\u7871 t, c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i ngh\u297  c\'e1ch t\u7921  c\u7913 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u th\u7917  m\u7897 t bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p c\'f3 l\u7869  h\u417 i ngu ng\u7889 c nh\u432 ng m\u7873 m m\u7887 ng, \'edt nh\u7845 t l\'fac \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t Alex bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7915 a d\u7883 p kh\'fac nh\u7841 c gi\'e1n \u273 o\u7841 n, c\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u d\'f9ng \'e2m l\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7921 c nh\u7887  n\'f3i v\u7899 i con qu\u7927  \u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean ph\u7843 i ph\'eda sau: "C\'e1c ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7909 ng \u273 \u7871 n t\'f4i, c\'e1c ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 bi\u7871 t Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'f4ng th\uc0\u7845 y con qu\u7927  kia nh\'edu nh\'edu m\'e0y, h\u417 i nghi ng\u7901  c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n ch\'fang bi\u7871 t, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'f3 hi v\u7885 ng r\u7891 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t y\u7871 t h\u7847 u, c\u7889  l\u7845 y d\u361 ng kh\'ed n\'f3i: "Th\u7843  t\'f4i ra, t\'f4i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a h\u7855 n." M\u7863 c d\'f9 \u273 ang d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh n\'e0y, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'f3i ra t\u7915  cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng kia c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7907 ng v\'e0 x\u226 \u769 u h\'f4\u777 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i c\'e1ch b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'e1 g\u7847 n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ph\'e1t ra t\u7915 ng tr\u7853 n c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7841 o v\'e0 bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i c\u7889  n\'e9n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nghe th\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n h\'e0i hoang \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng t\u7913 c c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7845 t tr\'ean \u273 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean, tai qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u r\u7845 t th\'ednh, c\u7853 u t\u7921  cho l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng, t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y to\'e0n b\u7897 .\cb1 \
