\cb3 "V\uc0\u7883  \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia h\u7847 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng bao gi\u7901  ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i ngo\u7841 i gi\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng sao h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\'e0i \u7845 y?" C\u361 ng c\'f3 r\u7845 t ti\u7871 ng nghi v\u7845 n r\u7845 t nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\uc0\u7871 t b\u7885 n ch\'fang kh\'f4ng tin, c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i ngh\u297  c\'e1ch kh\'e1c. K\u7923  th\u7853 t t\u7915  lo\u7841 t s\u7921  ki\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3, bao g\u7891 m t\u7915  th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i v\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng tho\'e1ng \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a v\u7883  kia trong gi\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c h\u7859 n l\'e0 l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng t\'e0n nh\u7851 n, kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n, c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i l\u7841 i th\u7847 n b\'ed nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o. Gi\u7843  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a h\u7855 n so ra c\'f2n kh\'f3 h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i gi\u7843  th\'e0nh m\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c phong l\u432 u th\'e0nh t\'ednh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1ng ti\u7871 c b\'e2y gi\u7901  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u7845 u v\u7871 t g\'ec do \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\u432 u l\u7841 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mang chi\u7871 c \'e1o cho\'e0ng c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7845 t c\u7913  ch\u7913 ng c\u7913  n\'e0o ch\u7913 ng minh m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng ti\u7871 p x\'fac v\u7899 i h\u7855 n. Cho n\'ean l\u7915 a nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y s\u7869  kh\'f3 h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i l\u7915 a Alex l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7847 n ch\u7915  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, *l\'f9i l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  ti\u7871 n m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... \'cdt nh\u7845 t h\u7855 n r\u7845 t th\'edch h\'fat m\'e1u t\'f4i." L\u7847 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 n\u7917 a \u273 i\u7875 m n\'f3i d\u7889 i.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (*Nguy\'ean v\uc0\u259 n 
\f4\i0 \'91\'de\'8e\'a7\'8b\'81\'91\'b4\'8e\'9f
\f2\i  (th\uc0\u7889 i nhi c\u7847 u k\u7923  th\u7913 ): mang ngh\u297 a kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7907 i \'edch cao nh\u7845 t ban \u273 \u7847 u, th\'ec c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7907 i \'edch t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i.)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7913 ng sau c\u7853 u ch\u7881  d\'f9ng \'e1nh m\u7855 t t\u7889 i \u273 en khinh th\u432 \u7901 ng li\u7871 c c\u7853 u: "Tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u417 i t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c danh t\u7921  kia, nh\u432 ng n\'f3i d\u7889 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\'fap ng\u432 \u417 i ch\u7871 t nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\u417 n \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "O\uc0\u7855 t con, l\u7847 n sau t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t ng\u432 \u417 i n\'ean nghe ng\'f3ng cho r\'f5 v\'e0o." H\u7855 n nh\u7871 ch m\'f4i, n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i t\'e0n \'e1c m\'e0 tr\'e0o ph\'fang, "To\'e0n b\u7897  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 t, v\u7883  \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p h\'fat m\'e1u t\u7915  c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m m\u7855 t, b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u n\'f3i th\u7853 t ai c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng tin r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  khi b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\u7883  b\u7855 t \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  th\u7901 i gian \u273 \'e3 qua bao l\'e2u? Hai ti\u7871 ng? Ba ti\u7871 ng? Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra m\'ecnh g\u7863 p b\u7845 t tr\u7855 c ch\u432 a? H\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  v\u7915 a k\u7883 p l\'fac li\'ean h\u7879  th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  t\u7899 i c\u7913 u m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng? N\u7871 u h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao? N\u7871 u h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p \u273 \u7871 n th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao? Ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'e2y?\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9i nh\uc0\u7885 n ba c\u7841 nh l\'f3e h\'e0n quang d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n, m\u7863 t tr\'ean tho\'e1ng d\'ednh n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7885 ng m\'e0u \u273 en, nh\u432  m\'e1u \u273 \u7885 ng th\'e0nh v\u7879 t b\u7849 n, b\'e1o hi\u7879 u v\u7853 n m\u7879 nh t\'e0n kh\u7889 c s\u7855 p \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Mang danh ti\uc0\u7871 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ra kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ch\u7881  tr\'f4ng ch\u7901  v\'e0o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ngh\u297  c\'e1ch, ngh\u297  c\'e1ch tr\u7889 n ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y, \'edt nh\u7845 t tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean ph\u7843 i gi\u7919  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'ednh m\u7841 ng... D\u7921 a v\'e0o v\u361  l\u7921 c th\'ec ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875 , ch\u432 a k\u7875  b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u c\'f2n \u273 ang b\u7883  tr\'f3i hai tay, cho d\'f9 c\u7853 u t\u7913  chi linh ho\u7841 t c\u361 ng kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 \u7845 u kh\'f4ng l\u7841 i nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  t\u7889  ch\u7845 t c\u417  th\u7875  v\u432 \u7907 t xa th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'e2n, xu\u7845 t qu\u7927  nh\u7853 p th\u7847 n kia...\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7847 u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u th\u7847 n t\u7889 c m\'f4 ph\u7887 ng c\'e1c thao t\'e1c, tr\'ean tr\'e1n th\u7845 m ra m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng m\u7891  h\'f4i m\u7887 ng, men theo g\'f2 m\'e1 tr\u432 \u7907 t xu\u7889 ng, r\u417 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t. B\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c sau m\u7897 t n\u7889 t cao, kh\'fac nh\u7841 c \u273 \'e3 d\u7847 n \u273 \u7871 n \u273 o\u7841 n k\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, \u273 ang mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 n \'fd ngh\u297  th\'e0nh h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng, ch\u7907 t c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t tay nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \'f4m eo c\u7853 u \'97\'97 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng ph\'eda sau, th\'e2n m\u7853 t k\u7873  s\'e1t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng c\u7903 i b\u7887  t\u7915 ng v\'f2ng b\u259 ng d\'ednh tr\'f3i hai tay m\'ecnh, c\u7847 m hai c\u7893  tay b\u7883  tr\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n run l\'ean nh\'e9t v\'e0o l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng xoa \u7845 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t, t\u7915  t\u7915  quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng n\u417 i t\u7889 i ph\'eda sau, h\u7841  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t h\u7855 n d\'f9ng th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n g\'ec, \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng con qu\u7927  n\'e0o ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n s\u7921  hi\u7879 n h\u7919 u c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ai ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n h\u7855 n l\u7867 n v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c quay \u273 \u7847 u c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t ch\'fa ng\u7919 , trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t ph\'e1 v\u7905  c\'e2n b\u7857 ng vi di\u7879 u tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 K\uc0\u7867  h\'e0nh h\'ecnh b\'ean ph\u7843 i ph\'eda sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u432  v\u7915 a m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra b\'ean tr\'e1i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\'eam m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\'e0y ra t\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng. Nam nh\'e2n m\u7863 c \'e1o cho\'e0ng d\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en, t\'f3c \u273 en ngay ng\u7855 n m\'e0 t\u7921  nhi\'ean r\u7911  xu\u7889 ng cu\u7889 i vai, h\u7855 n d\'f9ng m\u7897 t tay \u273 \u7905  h\'f4ng nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t y\'ean l\u7863 ng m\'e0 tr\u7847 m t\u297 nh. M\u7863 t h\u7855 n h\u417 i tr\u7855 ng, l\'fac \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3 \'f4m nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i kia th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  m\'e0 li\u7871 m r\u259 ng tr\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'fac nh\uc0\u7841 c \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ng\u7915 ng. Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e0i c\u361 ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i d\u7883  bi\u7871 n b\'ean n\'e0y, \u273 \u7891 ng lo\u7841 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  m\u7897 t ph\'eda, nh\'ecn k\u7867  kh\'f4ng m\u7901 i m\'e0 t\u7899 i l\u7867 n v\'e0o kia. Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m l\u7867 n v\'e0o h\u7855 n hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean \u273 \'e3 t\u7853 n l\u7921 c thu l\u7841 i kh\'ed t\u7913 c tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\'e0m b\u7885 n ch\'fang kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n ra c\u7845 p b\u7853 c v\'e0 th\'e2n ph\u7853 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, nh\u432 ng ch\'fang v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng nh\'ecn ra nam nh\'e2n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng th\'e2n m\u7853 t v\u7899 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i b\u7883  b\u7885 n ch\'fang b\u7855 t t\u7899 i l\'e0m t\u7871  ph\u7849 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u432 \u417 i l\'e0 ai? Ng\u432 \u417 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y l\'e0m g\'ec?" K\u7867  h\'e0nh h\'ecnh c\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\u7887 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n n\'e0y. Tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c d\u432 \u7905 ng th\'e0nh h\u417 n tr\u259 m qua c\u7911 a g\'e3 n\'f3i cho g\'e3 bi\u7871 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ta \uc0\u273 \u7871 n mang h\u7855 n \u273 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, l\u7841 i b\u7887  qua c\'e2u h\u7887 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c. Qu\u7923  tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t qu\'e1 l\'e2u, ch\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 t\'ea r\u7847 n, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7863 ng l\u7869  n\u7917 a d\u7921 a v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432  ph\'e1t gi\'e1c ra \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y, \'e1nh m\u7855 t t\u7889 i t\u259 m, \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c c\'e0ng ch\u7863 t h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\'ecn quanh \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh h\'ecnh b\u7847 u d\u7909 c m\u7897 t v\'f2ng, y\'ean l\u7863 ng m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "Theo ta \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bi\u7871 t, t\u7871  t\u7921  thu\u7847 n huy\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  c\u7845 m t\u7915  hai tr\u259 m n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7855 c m\u7863 t k\u7867  h\'e0nh h\'ecnh c\'e0ng th\'eam c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c: "Ng\u432 \u417 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tho\'e1ng d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, v\u7851 n b\'ecnh th\u7843 n tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7867  h\'e0nh h\'ecnh h\u417 i y\'ean t\'e2m. H\u7855 n bi\u7871 t, m\u432 \u7901 i ba \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p ch\u7883 u tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y ch\u7855 c s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ph\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ki\u7875 m tra b\u7885 n ch\'fang. N\u7871 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7899 i v\u7915 a v\'e0o \u273 \u7897 i kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u quy c\u7911 , b\u7885 n ch\'fang c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\'e1o hu\u7845 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat. Nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m \u273 \u7871 n hai m\u432 \u417 i t\u7899 i th\'ec s\u7869  c\'f3 ch\'fat phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u n\u7871 u \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 d\'e1m \u273 \u417 n th\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7897 c m\'e3 t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7901 i h\u7855 n "L\u432 u l\u7841 i", ch\u7859 ng qua vi\u7879 c x\u7917  l\'fd ti\u7871 p sau \u273 \'f3 e r\u7857 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng n\u7871 u \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng ng\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'f4ng th\uc0\u7845 y k\u7867  h\'e0nh h\'ecnh v\u7899 i kh\'f4ng \'edt qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7873 u l\u7897  ra n\'e9t m\u7863 t th\u7903  ph\'e0o nh\u7865  nh\'f5m. C\u7853 u c\'f3 ch\'fat s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t, tuy r\u7857 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7897  d\u7841 ng \u273 \'e3 t\'ednh tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n h\u7871 t s\u7913 c l\u7907 i h\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n ch\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  l\'e0 gi\u7887 i gi\u7843  v\u7901 . N\u7871 u b\u7883  \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  n\'e0y bao v\'e2y, ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n c\u7913 u m\'ecnh, ch\u7881  s\u7907  h\u7855 n c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i ng\u7887 m \u7903  \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7897  d\u7841 ng nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  kia r\'f5 r\'e0ng r\u7845 t ki\'eang k\u7883  \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i n\u7871 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7841 o nh\u7853 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'f3 th\u7875  tranh th\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'edt \u432 u th\u7871  cho b\'ean m\'ecnh. T\'ecnh h\'ecnh \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 kh\u7849 n c\u7845 p th\u7871  n\'e0y r\u7891 i, v\'ec sao Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f2n mu\u7889 n th\'e0nh th\u7853 t th\u7871  ch\u7913 ? Ng\u7851 m ngh\u297  l\u7841 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  th\'edch m\u7841 nh mi\u7879 ng, th\u7853 t ra ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng l\u7915 a g\u7841 t c\u7853 u, th\u7853 m ch\'ed m\u7845 y l\u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7853 u cho l\'e0 kho\'e1c l\'e1c c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 s\u7921  th\u7853 t. L\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean v\'ec ph\u7849 m ch\u7845 t t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\'e0 hoan h\'f4 khen ng\u7907 i hay l\'e0 th\u7903  d\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  gi\'e2y l\'e1t sau \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i r\'f5 r\'e0ng xao \u273 \u7897 ng, \u273 \u7891 ng lo\u7841 t ph\'e1t ra \'e2m thanh b\u7845 t m\'e3n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c t\u7921  \'fd l\u7867 n v\'e0o qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u bu\u7893 i t\u7871  t\u7921  kia, y\'eau c\u7847 u k\u7867  h\'e0nh h\'ecnh tr\'ean \u273 \'e0i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c tr\u7915 ng ph\u7841 t h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c ch\u7881  v\'e0o Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\u7899 n ti\u7871 ng qu\'e1t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 t\u7871  ph\u7849 m ch\'fang ta b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ng\u432 \u417 i d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 mu\u7889 n mang \u273 i? \u272 \u7875  n\'f3 l\u7841 i! Nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n, ng\u432 \u417 i c\u361 ng \u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y lu\'f4n \u273 i!"\cb1 \
\cb3 Truy\uc0\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t n\'f3i d\'f9ng m\'e1u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7875  t\u7871  s\u7869  c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  t\u7889 t h\u417 n. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m qua b\u7885 n ch\'fang \u273 \'e3 thu li\u7877 m l\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7841  th\u7911  trong n\u7897 i b\u7897  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. B\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng n\u7871 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  khi\'eau kh\'edch Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7845 p cao ch\'fa \'fd, ph\'e1i c\u7843  \u273 \u7897 i \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p t\u7899 i tra x\'e9t th\'ec s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f9a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn nh\'ecn theo h\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng \'e2m thanh, c\u7853 u c\'f3 \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\'ean ti\u7871 ng kia, l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong b\u7889 n con qu\u7927  b\u7855 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u, \u273 \u7905  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7841 nh B\u7841 ch Thu, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u d\u7863 n d\'f2 m\u7897 t c\'e2u, v\u7895  v\u7895  l\u432 ng c\u7853 u, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 i th\u7859 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t con qu\u7927  n\u7885 , t\u7915  tr\'ean cao nh\'ecn xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "Ng\u432 \u417 i mu\u7889 n c\u7843 n ta mang h\u7855 n \u273 i? V\u7853 y l\'e0m theo l\u7879  c\u361  \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\u7871 ch kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng, \'e1nh m\u7855 t s\'e2u \u273 en l\u7841 i tr\u7847 m t\u297 nh, nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e1y: "Hi\u7879 p \u273 \u7883 nh m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng nghe r\'f5 l\uc0\u7855 m l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i, ch\u7881  th\u7915 a c\u417  l\'e9n v\'f2ng qua c\u7903 i d\'e2y tr\'f3i cho B\u7841 ch Thu, ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m xu\u7889 ng v\u7895  nh\u7865  m\u7863 t c\'f4 b\u7841 n gi\'fap c\'f4 kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c \'fd th\u7913 c. Ch\u7901  B\u7841 ch Thu m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra li\u7873 n l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y lo l\u7855 ng nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \'e1nh m\u7855 t t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i kh\'f4ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i th\'e2n \u7843 nh m\'e0u \u273 en kia, B\u7841 ch Thu sau khi h\u7891 i t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i k\'e9o \'e1o c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7845 p th\u7845 p nghe v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i x\'f4n xao. Tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y, n\u7871 u hai Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i ch\u7885 n tr\'fang m\u7897 t con m\u7891 i th\'ec th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  d\'f9ng hi\u7879 p \u273 \u7883 nh m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh quy\u7873 n s\u7903  h\u7919 u. Song ph\u432 \u417 ng quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 u, b\'ean th\u7855 ng s\u7869  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c to\'e0n quy\u7873 n s\u7903  h\u7919 u con m\u7891 i. Nh\u432 ng theo th\u7901 i \u273 \u7841 i ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n kh\'f4ng c\'f2n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c v\'ec con m\u7891 i l\'e0m m\'e0 tranh gi\'e0nh nhau, hi\u7879 p \u273 \u7883 nh m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i c\u7893  x\u432 a c\u361 ng d\u7847 n kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t bao ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7841 i b\u7883  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7871 n khi\'eau kh\'edch nh\u432  th\u7871 . R\u259 ng nanh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u hi\u7879 n ra, g\'e3 c\u7903 i m\u7863 t n\u7841  n\'e9m xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, tho\u7855 t c\'e1i nh\u7843 y l\'ean \u273 \'e0i. \u272 \u7897 ng t\'e1c n\'e0y t\u7887  r\'f5 g\'e3 \u273 \'e3 ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n hi\u7879 p \u273 \u7883 nh m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e0i l\'e0 ti\u7871 ng v\u7895  tay v\'e0 ti\u7871 ng h\'f2 reo c\u7893  v\u361  \u273 i\'ean cu\u7891 ng, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng la h\'e9t th\'fac gi\u7909 c. Nh\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kia d\'e1m ch\u7855 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7867 n v\'e0o n\'e0y cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng s\u7869  ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i m\'e1u v\'e0 m\u7841 ng, tr\u7903  th\'e0nh t\u7871  ph\u7849 m th\u7913  m\u432 \u7901 i hai t\u7889 i nay, b\u7885 n ch\'fang \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\'e2u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7871 m th\u7917  t\u7871  ph\u7849 m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. Tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac \u273 \'f3 ch\'fang kh\'f4ng ng\u7841 i xem th\'eam \'edt tr\'f2 hay, d\'f9ng ti\u7871 t m\u7909 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  gi\u7843 i t\u7887 a tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i \u273 i\'ean cu\u7891 ng v\'e0 k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m l\u7845 y ra t\u7915  trong t\'fai \'e1o m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c g\u259 ng tay l\u7909 a m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng \u273 eo l\'ean, v\u7915 a kh\u7869  nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 tr\'e1nh kh\u7887 i c\'f4ng k\'edch c\u7911 a con qu\u7927  kia. V\u7841 t \'e1o cho\'e0ng \u273 en bay l\'ean theo \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, l\'fac tay tr\'e1i h\u7841  xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 n n\u7919 a \u273 \'e3 b\'f3p ch\u7863 t y\u7871 t h\u7847 u con qu\u7927  n\u7885 , nh\u7845 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'ean kh\u7887 i m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  ch\u7881  ph\'e1t sinh trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'e9t m\uc0\u7863 t h\u7855 n v\u7851 n r\u7845 t th\u7843 n nhi\'ean, kh\'f4ng ch\'fat g\u7907 n s\'f3ng, nh\'ecn qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t nh\u432  nh\'ecn m\u7897 t v\u7853 t b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u l\'e0 v\u7853 t ch\u7871 t. H\u7855 n th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn con qu\u7927 , t\u7847 m m\u7855 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 l\u432 \u7899 t qua ng\u432 \u7901 i trong tay chuy\u7875 n h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i y\'ean t\u297 nh tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn ch\u259 m ch\u259 m m\u7897 t m\'e0n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t. \u272 \'e3 c\'f3 ng\'e0y c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\'ean \u273 \'e0i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e0n tay gh\'ecm c\u7893  m\'ecnh \u273 ang kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng si\u7871 t ch\u7863 t, nh\u432  m\u7897 t gi\'e2y sau s\u7869  b\'f3p \u273 \u7913 t c\u7893  h\u7885 ng c\u7911 a g\'e3. Cho d\'f9 l\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, \u273 \u7913 t c\u7893  c\u361 ng s\u7869  "Ch\u7871 t", khi \u273 \'f3 ch\'ednh l\'e0 l\u7847 n th\u7913  hai, th\u7853 t s\u7921  ho\'e0n to\'e0n t\u7917  vong.\cb1 \
\cb3 G\'e3 c\uc0\u7889  s\u7913 c ph\'e1t ra \'e2m thanh t\u7915  trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng: "S\'e1t th\'e2n... L\'e0 t\u7917  t\u7897 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7853 t sao?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u sang tr\'e1i, c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i, "Nh\u432 ng th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ta gi\u7871 t Derek kh\'f4ng ai n\'f3i cho ta bi\u7871 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m c\uc0\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7855 n r\u7845 t nh\u7887 , l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, B\u7841 ch Thu Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  m\'e9p \u273 \'e0i nh\'ecn c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng to\'e0n b\u7897  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 nghe th\u7845 y. C\'e1i t\'ean "Derek" n\'e0y nh\u432  m\u7897 t ng\u7885 n s\'e9t n\u7893  vang tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u b\u7885 n ch\'fang. Derek \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t ngh\'ecn n\u259 m \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m h\'f3a th\'e0nh c\'e1t b\u7909 i, nh\u432 ng c\'e1i t\'ean Derek v\u7851 n th\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta li\'ean t\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n v\u7883  kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe n\'f3i thu\uc0\u7903  x\u432 a cha h\u7855 n l\'e0 Qu\u7889 c v\u432 \u417 ng m\u7897 t n\u432 \u7899 c, m\'e0 m\u7865  h\u7855 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng t\'ecnh nh\'e2n c\u7911 a Qu\u7889 c v\u432 \u417 ng, nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec v\u7867  ngo\'e0i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \'f4ng xinh \u273 \u7865 p m\'e0 hi\u7871 m th\u7845 y n\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7911 ng \'e1i. H\u7855 n l\'e0 con trai tr\u432 \u7903 ng, sau khi sinh ra li\u7873 n b\u7883  coi l\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 m x\u7845 u, c\u361 ng b\u7883  qu\u7843  quy\u7871 t l\'e0 kh\'f4ng s\u7889 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u, b\u7903 i tim h\u7855 n \u273 \u7853 p r\u7845 t ch\u7853 m, c\u361 ng r\u7845 t y\u7871 u \u7899 t, \u273 \'f4i khi th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'e0ng l\u7899 n, nh\u7883 p tim v\'e0 m\u7841 ch \u273 \u7853 p c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\'e0ng tr\u7903  n\'ean m\u7887 ng manh. C\'e0ng th\'eam k\u7923  d\u7883  l\'e0 \u273 \u7891  \u259 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, h\u7855 n ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7921 a v\'e0o u\u7889 ng m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t \u273 \u7875  duy tr\'ec sinh m\u7879 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7889 c v\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng th\'edch \u273 \u7913 a con ri\'eang t\'e0 d\u7883  n\'e0y, sau khi h\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c sinh ra kh\'f4ng l\'e2u li\u7873 n \u273 em hai m\u7865  con giam v\'e0o trong m\u7897 t t\'f2a th\'e0nh. M\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m h\u7855 n c\'f2n \u7845 u ni\'ean, m\u7865  h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 bu\'f4ng tay th\u7871  gian.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n d\u7847 n l\u7899 n l\'ean, h\'e0nh vi ng\'e0y th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng nh\u7883 p tim l\u7841 i ng\'e0y t\u7915 ng ng\'e0y d\u7847 n d\u7847 n g\u7847 n nh\u432  d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i. L\'fac \u7845 y Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\u7841 nh nh\u7845 t ch\'e2u \'c2u \'96 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Derek nghe n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, d\u7921  c\u7843 m sau khi h\u7855 n ch\u7871 t \u273 i s\u7869  t\u7921  nhi\'ean chuy\u7875 n h\'f3a th\'e0nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \'97\'97 m\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c thu\u7847 n huy\u7871 t nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a th\u7871  h\u7879  thu\u7847 n huy\u7871 t \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean, cho n\'ean mu\u7889 n ti\u7871 n h\'e0nh s\u417  \u7911 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac h\u7855 n t\u7855 t th\u7903 , chuy\u7875 n h\'f3a h\u7855 n l\'e0m h\u7853 u du\u7879  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \

