\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c v\u7851 n lu\'f4n d\'f9ng tr\'e1i tay \'f4m eo Tr\'ec Di\'ean, b\'e0n tay \u7849 n trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i gi\u7845 u d\u432 \u7899 i tay \'e1o, \u273 \'e1m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c xao \u273 \u7897 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t k\u7867 o n\'e0o ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n tr\'ean tay h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
