\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tho\'e1ng si\u7871 t n\u259 m ng\'f3n tay, \'e1nh m\u7855 t r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nhu h\'f2a m\'e0 tri\u7873 n mi\'ean m\'e0 nh\'ecn v\u7873  n\u417 i kh\'e1c: "... Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\'e1c ng\u432 \u417 i r\u7891 i sao, h\u7855 n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a ta..."\cb1 \
