\cf2 \cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'e9m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \'e3 t\u7855 t th\u7903  qua m\u7897 t b\'ean, m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i th\u7859 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e0i t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7873 u c\'fai th\u7845 p \u273 \u7847 u, nh\u7889 n nh\'e1o tr\'e1nh sang hai b\'ean, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m li\u7871 c h\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7853 n n\'e0y \u273 \'e1nh qu\'e1 nhanh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a m\u7899 i k\u7883 p lo l\u7855 ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  v\u7873 . C\u7853 u ng\u7917 a \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927 , h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng: "Anh..." sao \u273 \'e3 quay l\u7841 i r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, m\'f4i nh\u432  l\u417  \u273 \'e3ng l\u432 \u7899 t qua \u273 \u7881 nh \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0 tr\'e1n c\u7853 u. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng h\u7855 n gh\'e9 v\'e0o b\'ean tai Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i: "T\'f4i \u273 \'e1nh c\u432 \u7907 c v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 . T\'f4i th\u7855 ng, t\'f4i s\u7869  d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u qu\u7843  th\u7853 t th\u7855 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  mang ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t \u273 i, t\u7915  nay v\u7873  sau tri\u7879 t tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7875  ch\u7881  thu\u7897 c v\u7873  m\'ecnh . . . V\u7853 y r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng t\u7879 . Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c li\u7871 m li\u7871 m r\u259 ng, t\'e2m t\'ecnh lay \u273 \u7897 ng m\'e0 m\u417  m\u7897 ng. H\u7855 n nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  gi\u7845 u k\u7929  ph\u7847 n th\u432 \u7903 ng nh\u7887  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, th\u7901 i th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c kh\u7855 c \u273 \u7873 u b\u7845 t ly th\'e2n, ban ng\'e0y n\'e2ng trong tay, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i \'f4m ch\u7863 t v\'e0o l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c xung quanh, t\u7845 t c\u7843  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7873 u c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u ph\u7909 c t\'f9ng \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, k\u7867  h\'e0nh h\'ecnh v\u7889 n c\'e1ch b\u7885 n h\u7885  g\u7847 n nh\u7845 t \u273 \'e3 bu\'f4ng ch\'f9y th\'e9p trong tay, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u qu\u7923  tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7897  d\u7841 ng th\u7871  kia m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 th\u7855 ng c\u432 \u7907 c. C\u7853 u kh\u7869  nh\'edu m\'e0y, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean k\'e9o tay tr\'e1i c\u7853 u, th\'e1o nh\u7851 n tr\'ean ng\'f3n \'e1p \'fat m\'ecnh xu\u7889 ng, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n \u273 eo l\'ean ng\'f3n \'e1p \'fat tay c\u7853 u, t\u7887  v\u7867  nh\u432  th\u7901  \u417 : "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, c\'e1i n\'e0y cho c\u7853 u. \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 t\'edn v\u7853 t c\u7911 a t\'f4i, cho c\u7853 u, c\'f3 l\u7869  th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng s\u7869  c\'f3 ch\'fat t\'e1c d\u7909 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'edn v\uc0\u7853 t? Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\'f2 m\'f2 x\'f2e n\u259 m ng\'f3n tay b\'ean tr\'e1i m\'ecnh, th\'e0nh c\'f4ng b\u7883  d\u7901 i l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd, t\u7841 m th\u7901 i \u273 \'e8 xu\u7889 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng trong l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7851 n ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n m\'e0 trang nghi\'eam, h\'ecnh v\u7869  b\u7909 i gai hoa h\u7891 ng ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a c\u361 ng r\u7845 t kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t, ch\u7863 t ch\u7869  \'f4m ng\'f3n tay c\u7853 u, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  v\'ec c\u7853 u m\'e0 ch\u7871  t\u7841 o. C\u7853 u th\u7917  d\'f9ng tay ph\u7843 i r\'fat ra, chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sao c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  ch\u7913 , c\u7853 u c\u7847 m tay tr\'e1i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'ean c\u7849 n th\u7853 n xem x\'e9t, l\u7841 i du\u7895 i tay m\'ecnh ra so s\'e1nh v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, ng\'f3n tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\u7899 n h\u417 n m\'ecnh m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  th\'e1o xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, v\'ec sao m\'ecnh l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, m\u7863 c c\u7853 u h\u7891  nh\'e1o, ch\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean x\u7845 u h\u7893  m\'e0 ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng bu\'f4ng tay ra h\u7855 n m\u7899 i k\'e9o tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i, ch\u7881  v\'e0o chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n m\'e0u b\u7841 c n\'f3i: "B\u7903 i v\'ec l\'e0 t\'edn v\u7853 t, cho n\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 t\'f4i m\u7899 i th\'e1o ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i xong g\u7853 p ng\'f3n tay c\u7853 u l\u7841 i n\u7855 m th\'e0nh quy\u7873 n, bao trong l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay, nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng d\u7863 n d\'f2: "C\u7845 t c\u7849 n th\u7853 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t tay tr\'e1i, kh\'f4ng kh\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915  n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en r\u7845 t nghi\'eam t\'fac, c\u361 ng r\u7845 t ch\'e2n th\'e0nh tha thi\u7871 t, l\u7859 ng l\u7863 ng ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, t\u7921 a nh\u432  c\u361 ng mang t\'e2m m\'ecnh ra giao ph\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean h\u417 i ng\u432 \u7907 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng chuy\u7875 n t\u7847 m m\u7855 t, \u273 \'fang l\'fac th\u7845 y thi th\u7875  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\'ean kia b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'e9m tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t: ". . . Anh gi\u7871 t h\u7855 n r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i l\'e0 th\uc0\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u m\'e0." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, "S\u7869  lu\'f4n c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\'e0i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7897 t ph\'e1t d\u432 \u7899 i quy\u7873 n h\u7841 n. Kh\'f4ng l\'e0m v\u7853 y sao t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7843  k\'edch t\'ednh hung h\u259 ng ki\'eau ng\u7841 o c\u7911 a b\u7885 n ch\'fang, l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  mang c\u7853 u \u273 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y b\'e2y gi\u7901  b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  th\u7843  ch\'fang ta \u273 i sao?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i, c\u7853 u nh\'ecn ch\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \'fd th\u7913 c v\u7851 n ch\u432 a thanh t\u7881 nh l\u7855 m c\u7841 nh B\u7841 ch Thu, "Em l\'e0 n\'f3i, ch\'fang ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7847 n ra kh\u7887 i n\u417 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 ri\'eang hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 . Nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 th\u7875  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i h\u7871 t kh\'f4ng? B\u7885 n ch\'fang sao c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng bu\'f4ng tha b\u7885 n h\u7885  nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7913 ? Nh\u432 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e3y gi\u7901  l\u7841 i quay tr\u7903  v\u7873 , nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  m\u7899 i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\'f2n v\'f4 c\'f9ng c\'e0n r\u7905  kia v\'ec sao l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7903  n\'ean th\'e0nh th\u7853 t, v\u7843  l\u7841 i. . . cung k\'ednh nh\u432  th\u7871 . Gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang s\u7907  h\'e3i \u273 i\u7873 u g\'ec \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng th\'ec th\u7847 m n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean. T\'f4i \u273 \'e2u c\'f3 ngu ng\u7889 c, t\'f4i c\'f3 mang ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y, cho n\'ean b\u7885 n ch\'fang kh\'f4ng d\'e1m kh\'f4ng th\u7843  ch\'fang ta \u273 i."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u kinh ng\u7841 c nh\'ecn h\u7855 n. Ch\u7881  th\u7845 y h\u7855 n v\u7915 a d\u7913 t l\u7901 i, l\u7841 i c\'f3 m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 y th\'e2n \u7843 nh \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n trong \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 b\u7889 n n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng tr\'ean \u273 \u7881 nh m\'e1i v\'f2m, bao v\'e2y to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  m\'e0u \u273 en th\u7889 ng nh\u7845 t, ch\'e2n \u273 eo gi\'e0y b\'f3 \u273 en, quanh th\'e2n mang s\'e1t kh\'ed l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o, Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7847 n nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c huy\u7871 t kh\'ed tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f2n n\u7891 ng \u273 \u7853 m h\u417 n tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c\'97\'97tr\'ean tay b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u nhu\u7897 m m\'e1u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c d\'e1n b\'ean tai c\u7853 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch: "Sau khi \u273 o\'e1n c\u7853 u g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng may, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean t\'f4i \u273 i t\'ecm c\u7853 u, sau \u273 \'f3 b\'e1o tin cho ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 p \u7913 ng." Chuy\u7879 n gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t h\u7853 u qu\u7843  d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m.\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e0 \uc0\u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c anh nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean kinh ng\u7841 c nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, "Anh l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 c\'f3 quan h\u7879 . . . m\u7853 t thi\u7871 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y v\u7899 i h\u7885 ?" M\u7863 c d\'f9 n\'f3i th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  sau khi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n h\'e0nh vi sai tr\'e1i c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c , tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  t\u7889  gi\'e1c cho \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c x\u7917  l\'fd, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u n\'f3i t\u7915 ng c\'f3 giao thi\u7879 p, c\'f3 ch\'fat giao t\'ecnh th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7907 p l\'fd. Suy cho c\'f9ng d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng ngay c\u7843  ch\u7913 ng c\u7913  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3, \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p d\u7921 a v\'e0o c\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 ch\u7881  b\u7903 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1i nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\u7899 i ti\u7871 p \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng, " Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean c\u361 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c ph\u7843 i gi\u7843 i th\'edch v\'ec sao h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nhanh ch\'f3ng \u273 i\u7873 u \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7897 c l\u7853 p, v\u7889 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c, cho n\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\u7901 i l\u7869  ch\'ednh \u273 \'e1ng ph\u7911  nh\u7853 n n\'f3i, "L\u7847 n n\'e0y \u273 i c\'f9ng t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\'e0 l\'e0 \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927 . Th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  c\u361 ng c\'f3 \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u7847 m l\u7845 y tay tr\'e1i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng s\u7901  chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n tr\'ean tay c\u7853 u, \'e1nh m\u7855 t nhu h\'f2a m\'e0 nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "C\u7853 u ph\u7843 i tin t\u432 \u7903 ng t\'f4i l\'e0 m\u7897 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u... m\u7897 t th\u7907  s\u259 n c\'f3 v\u7853 t l\'e0m tin, c\'f3 quy\u7873 n c\'f3 th\u7871 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y anh c\u361 ng l\'e0 th\'e0nh vi\'ean trong \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p sao?" V\u7915 a r\u7891 i ph\u7911  nh\u7853 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n t\u7915  \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\'ec mu\u7889 n k\u7867  \u273 \u7883 ch l\u417  l\'e0 ch\u7911  quan?\cb1 \
\cb3 ". . . Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tho\'e1ng d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, th\'e0nh th\u7853 t \u273 \'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn nh\'ecn c\'e1c th\'e0nh vi\'ean trong \uc0\u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p b\u7889 n ph\'eda \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh, kh\'ed th\u7871  l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng nghi\'eam t\'fac, m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  th\u7889 ng nh\u7845 t, m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng bi\u7875 u t\'ecnh, nh\'ecn qua v\'f4 c\'f9ng l\u7907 i h\u7841 i, l\u7841 i nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \'f4n nhu nh\'ecn m\'ecnh. So s\'e1nh hai b\'ean, nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u ra v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 : "Kh\'f4ng sao, sau n\'e0y anh tr\u7903  n\'ean l\u7907 i h\u7841 i r\u7891 i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  gia nh\u7853 p b\u7885 n h\u7885 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7921 c l\u7921 c hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\'f2n qu\'e1 y\u7871 u cho n\'ean m\u7899 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m nh\'e2n vi\'ean ngo\'e0i bi\'ean ch\u7871 , kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e0m vi\u7879 c trong \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p. Nh\u432 ng nh\'ecn t\u7915  h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 u\u7893 i ng\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3i \u273 i l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f9ng l\u7847 n n\'e0y nhanh ch\'f3ng s\u259 n gi\u7871 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7845 p th\u7845 p, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng r\u7845 t l\u7907 i h\u7841 i, r\u7845 t c\'f3 ti\u7873 m n\u259 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7893  ti\'ean h\u7855 n c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 xu\u7845 t ra nh\u7919 ng th\u7907  s\u259 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng \u432 u t\'fa, gia t\u7897 c trong gi\u7899 i th\u7907  s\u259 n t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i c\'f3 danh v\u7885 ng, h\u7855 n m\u7899 i c\'f3 v\u7853 t gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\'edn v\u7853 t n\'e0y, nh\u7919 ng th\u7907  s\u259 n kh\'e1c c\u361 ng s\u7869  chi\u7871 u c\u7889  h\u7855 n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n ch\'fat. Chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n n\'e0y c\'f3 l\u7869  ch\'ednh l\'e0 bi\u7875 u t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a gia t\u7897 c nh\'e0 h\u7855 n, nh\u7919 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'e1c sau khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i trong gia t\u7897 c th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  l\u7907 i h\u7841 i, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\'f9y ti\u7879 n \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n h\u7855 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7901  chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n tr\'ean ng\'f3n tay m\'ecnh, t\'e2m m\u7873 m nh\u361 n, c\'e0ng th\'eam c\u7843 m \u273 \u7897 ng ghi nh\u7899  s\u7921  b\u7843 o v\u7879  c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi sau khi nghe v\u7853 y li\u7873 n tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c m\u7897 t l\'e1t, \'f4n nhu \u273 \'e1p, nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng vu\u7889 t nh\u7851 n, kh\'f3e m\u7855 t nhu h\'f2a kh\u7869  cong "T\'f4i s\u7869  c\u7889  g\u7855 ng tr\u7903  th\'e0nh th\u7907  s\u259 n \u432 u t\'fa h\u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1c th\'e0nh vi\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p th\u7913  hai m\u432 \u417 i \u273 i theo \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y l\'fac n\'e0y c\'f3 ch\'fat h\u7853 n v\'ec sao th\'ednh l\u7921 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\u7841 i t\u7889 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y \'97\'97 b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\u7917 a ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n nghe th\u7845 y \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u7889 i tho\u7841 i kinh h\'e3i, h\'f9 ch\u7871 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  c\'f9ng nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i h\u7855 n y\'eau th\'edch kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7899 i t\u432  c\'e1ch l\'e0 \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c chi\u7871 n t\'edch huy ho\'e0ng nh\u7845 t, b\u7885 n h\u7885  tuy\u7879 t kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  b\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  \u273 i th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t nhi\u7879 m v\u7909 , \u273 i\u7873 u tra m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 ang ti\u7871 n h\'e0nh t\u7871  t\u7921  thu\u7847 n huy\u7871 t, th\u7871  m\'e0 tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p b\u7883  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  qu\u7843  quy\u7871 t th\'e0nh th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u. B\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'f4 c\'f9ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7873 u n\'edn thinh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m khi\u7871 u n\u7841 i, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ph\u7843 n b\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng ch\'fang ta nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u432 ng ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7843  v\u7901  nh\u432  kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y. D\'f9 sao ch\'fang ta n\'e9t m\u7863 t g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3. Nh\'ecn \u273 i, \u273 \u7897 i tr\u432 \u7903 ng gi\u7887 i ch\u432 a, \u273 \'e3 l\u7915 a m\'ecnh d\u7889 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m nh\u432  chuy\u7879 n g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t sinh, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u v\u7863 n h\u7887 i \u273 \'e1m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c b\'ean kia r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f3m l\uc0\u7841 i hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  ch\u7895  n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  giao cho \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p, ch\'fang ta \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c th\'f4i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, "B\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  s\u7855 p x\u7871 p t\u7889 t cho nh\u7919 ng nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i c\'f2n l\u7841 i, x\'f3a tr\'ed nh\u7899  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 a v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, h\u417 i lo l\u7855 ng m\'e0 nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda B\u7841 ch Thu, B\u7841 ch Thu c\u361 ng \u273 ang kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng m\'e0 nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, hai tay b\u7845 t an n\u7855 m v\u7841 t \'e1o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n c\'f4 nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng tr\u7845 n an n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \'e2u, \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907 , s\u7869  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i x\'f3a tr\'ed nh\u7899  li\'ean quan c\u7911 a c\u7853 u r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y, c\u7853 u s\u7869  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nh\u432  m\u417  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i th\'ec \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  v\u7873  chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng quen thu\u7897 c, nh\u7919 ng k\'fd \u7913 c kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i hi\uc0\u7875 u m\'e0, nh\u432  phim Harry Potter \u7845 y, b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan gi\u7919  l\u7841 i tr\'ed nh\u7899 ." B\u7841 ch Thu g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  m\u7897 t c\'e1i, "Tuy r\u7857 ng t\'f4i m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n tr\'ed nh\u7899  c\u7911 a t\'f4i bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, b\u7845 t k\u7875  t\u7889 t x\u7845 u, kinh kh\u7911 ng hay vui v\u7867 , t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u mu\u7889 n gi\u7919  n\'f3 l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 t\'f2 m\'f2 nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Nh\uc0\u432 ng sao c\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\u7899  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y? C\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng, t\'f4i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra ngo\'e0i \u273 \'e2u, th\u7921 c t\u7871  d\'f9 sao l\'e1t n\u7919 a c\'f3 l\u7869  b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  l\'e0m t\'f4i qu\'ean \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "Ch\'ednh l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7845 y, \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7911 a t\'f4i v\'e0 v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng kia v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t. Ch\u7901  \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh ho\'e0n th\'e0nh, c\'f3 l\u7869  h\u7855 n c\u361 ng s\u7869  ti\'eau tr\u7915  tr\'ed nh\u7899  li\'ean quan c\u7911 a t\'f4i." Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn c\'f2n xa l\u7855 m, t\u7841 m th\u7901 i c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u432 a t\'ednh \u273 \u7871 n v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7841 ch Thu l\u7841 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i, c\'e1o bi\u7879 t v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u7913 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c nh\'ecn b\u7885 n h\u7885 , \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e1o bi\u7879 t nhau xong li\u7873 n \u273 \u432 a tay ra hi\u7879 u v\u7899 i m\u7897 t th\'e0nh vi\'ean \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng g\u7847 n nh\u7845 t, h\u7845 t c\u7857 m v\u7873  ph\'eda B\u7841 ch Thu, ra hi\u7879 u n\'f3i: "Ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 i \u273 \u432 a c\'f4 g\'e1i n\'e0y r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e0nh vi\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p kia nh\u7853 n l\u7879 nh \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t B\u7841 ch Thu, kh\u7869  c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i c\'f4: "M\u7901 i c\'f4 \u273 i theo t\'f4i, t\'f4i s\u7869  d\u7851 n c\'f4 ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7841 ch Thu l\u7841 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n duy nh\u7845 t \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, tuy r\u7857 ng tr\'ean m\u7863 t v\u7851 n mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng duy tr\'ec tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh, nh\u432 ng s\'e2u trong m\u7855 t v\u7851 n c\'f3 lo s\u7907  b\u7845 t an kh\'f4ng th\u7875  gi\u7845 u h\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i c\'f4, tr\u7845 n an g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, nh\'ecn b\u7841 n m\'ecnh ch\u7853 m r\'e3i \u273 i theo th\'e0nh vi\'ean \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i t\u7915  n\u417 i c\u7917 a nh\u7887  m\u7863 t sau \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh. C\u361 ng c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng th\'e0nh vi\'ean kh\'e1c l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t \u273 \u432 a nh\u7919 ng nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a t\u7881 nh t\'e1o \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'e9p k\'edn, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\u7917 a nh\u7887  \u7903  m\u7863 t sau, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\'e2y gi\u7901  b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 ang \u7903  d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, mu\u7889 n ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh kh\'e9p k\'edn n\'e0y c\'f2n ph\u7843 i \u273 i l\'ean m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng r\u7845 t d\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng u\u7889 n l\u432 \u7907 n quanh co h\u432 \u7899 ng xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i l\'fac m\'ecnh \u273 \u7871 n: "Anh c\u361 ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y nh\u432  th\u7871  sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, ch\u7881  v\u7851 y v\u7851 y tay v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, b\u7843 o c\u7853 u s\'e1t l\u7841 i g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng hi\uc0\u7875 u m\'f4 t\'ea g\'ec b\u432 \u7899 c v\u7873  ph\'eda h\u7855 n hai b\u432 \u7899 c. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "Ch\u432 a \u273 \u7911 , l\u7841 i g\u7847 n ch\'fat n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng n\u7871 u l\u7841 i g\u7847 n th\'eam th\'ec s\u7869  tr\u7903  th\'e0nh c\u7853 u \'e1p l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 a m\u7855 t nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch gi\u7919 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, do d\u7921  b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7907 i hai gi\'e2y, d\u7913 t kho\'e1t tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p v\u432 \u417 n tay k\'e9o c\u7853 u \u7845 n v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c \'f4m: "N\u7855 m ch\u7855 c, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, t\'f4i mang c\u7853 u ra ngo\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t h\u7855 n \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0m g\'ec, m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\'f2n kh\'f4ng nghe l\u7901 i m\'e0 m\'f9 t\u7883 t tr\u7907 n tr\'f2n m\u7855 t nh\'ecn m\u7863 t h\u7855 n, ngay sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c lu\u7891 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'ed quanh ng\u432 \u7901 i xoay tr\'f2n t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  cao, h\u417 n n\u7919 a t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng nhanh. C\u7853 u c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng nh\u7855 m ch\u7863 t m\u7855 t, g\u7855 t gao \'f4m l\u7845 y eo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
