\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mang Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'ean tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'e0nh, t\uc0\u432 \u417 i m\'e1t, c\'f3 ch\'fat gi\'f3 \u7849 m l\u432 \u7899 t qua m\u7863 t, th\u7893 i tan t\'f3c m\'e1i tr\'ean tr\'e1n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  m\u7855 t ra, nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\u7847 u tr\u7901 i \u273 \'eam xa x\'f4i m\'e0 s\'e2u th\u7859 m \u7903  nam b\'e1n c\u7847 u, nh\u7919 ng ng\'f4i sao r\u7845 t s\'e1ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\u7919 ng vi\'ean kim c\u432 \u417 ng l\u7845 p l\'e1nh, trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y tr\u7901 i \u273 \'eam s\'e1ng r\'f5 m\'e0 trong v\u7855 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'e0 khi c\'f2n nh\u7887 . Sau khi l\u7899 n l\'ean th\'ec \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\u7901 i gian r\u7843 nh r\u7895 i v\'e0 t\'e2m t\u432  ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u ng\u7855 m tr\u7901 i \u273 \'eam, d\'f9 cho ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn, th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng ng\'f4i sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\'f3 \uc0\u273 \'eam nh\'e8 nh\u7865 , hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang \u7903  tr\'ean m\u7897 t \u273 \u7891 ng c\u7887  kh\'f4ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u432 a m\u7855 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  n\u417 i xa c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\'f3 b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i hay ng\'f4i nh\'e0 n\'e0o, ch\u7881  c\'f3 c\u7887  xanh tr\u7843 i d\'e0i \u273 \u7871 n ch\'e2n tr\u7901 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n c\'f3 l\u7869  b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 ang \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 ngo\'e0i ngo\u7841 i \'f4.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c s\u7889 ng s\'f3t sau tai ki\u7871 p l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i cu\u7891 n cu\u7897 n k\'e9o t\u7899 i. C\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 eo m\u7863 t n\u7841  tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch, x\'ec x\'e0o b\'e0n t\'e1n, c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7863 c kh\u7863 c qu\'e1i d\u7883 ; nh\u7899  t\u7899 i kh\'fac nh\u7841 c du d\u432 \u417 ng u \'e1m; nh\u7899  t\u7899 i chi\u7871 c d\'f9i ba c\u7841 nh s\u7855 c nh\u7885 n sau l\u432 ng c\'f9ng v\u7899 i chi\u7871 c b\'f3ng r\u7845 t d\'e0i lay l\u7855 t, b\u7883  \'e1nh n\u7871 n ph\'f3ng \u273 \u7841 i...\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'e1i ch\u7871 t t\u7899 i g\u7847 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Cho d\'f9 \u7903  y\u7871 n h\u7897 i m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u7921  c\u7843 m "M\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  ch\u7871 t" m\'e3nh li\u7879 t \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 , th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t Emmer Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng, ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c c\u7853 u l\u7841 i c\'e0ng h\u7871 t l\'f2ng tin r\u7857 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  th\u432 \u417 ng t\u7893 n c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n \'f4m c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng, h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c \u273 ang kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng run r\u7849 y, r\u7845 t kh\u7869 , c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1i nh\'e2n trong l\'f2ng m\'ecnh \u273 ang kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng ph\'e1t run.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 ang s\u7907 . Nh\u7853 n ra \u273 i\u7873 u n\'e0y l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n tim Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi treo l\'ean, th\u432 \u417 ng x\'f3t \u273 au l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \'f4m ch\u7863 t hai tay, d\u7883 u d\'e0ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\'e0m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kinh ho\u7843 ng, kh\u7869  h\'f4n l\'ean t\'f3c l\'ean th\'e1i d\u432 \u417 ng c\u7853 u, th\'ec th\u7847 m tr\u7845 n an: "Xin l\u7895 i, ta sai r\u7891 i, l\'e0 ta kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, ta n\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n s\u7899 m h\u417 n... Ta cam \u273 oan s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u7847 n sau..." \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n v\u7899 i t\u432  c\'e1ch gi\u7889 ng \u273 \u7921 c, b\u7843 n n\u259 ng mu\u7889 n b\u7843 o v\u7879  b\u7841 n \u273 \u7901 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh m\u7885 i s\u7921  \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh an, kh\'f4ng b\u7883  b\u7845 t c\u7913  th\u432 \u417 ng t\u7893 n g\'ec, d\'f9 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7911  m\u7841 nh \u273 \u7875  t\u7921  b\u7843 o v\u7879  b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'ec c\u361 ng v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\uc0\u7899 i h\u7855 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng th\'ec th\u7847 m, d\u7921 a v\'e0o h\u7855 n trong ch\u7889 c l\'e1t, h\'edt s\'e2u hai h\u417 i, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i \u273 em to\'e0n b\u7897  t\'e2m tr\u7841 ng ti\'eau c\u7921 c v\u7915 a r\u7891 i gi\u7843 i t\u7887 a ra ngo\'e0i. C\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng \u7893 n, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, em nh\'ecn th\u7845 y h\'ecnh nh\u432  anh n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3 r\u7891 i gi\u7871 t t\'ean qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia, sau \u273 \'f3 nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  kh\'e1c li\u7873 n tr\u7903  n\'ean r\u7845 t cung k\'ednh r\u7845 t s\u7907  h\'e3i, m\u7897 t \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c nh\u7887  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m. V\'ec sao th\u7871 ? Anh \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i g\'ec v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n \u273 ang r\u7845 t \u273 au l\'f2ng m\'e0 s\u7901  t\'f3c x\'f5a tr\u432 \u7899 c tr\'e1n c\u7853 u nh\u432  s\u7901  l\'f4ng \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t, nghe v\u7853 y ch\u7881  thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "T\'f4i ch\u7881  l\'e0 n\'f3i cho b\u7885 n h\u7885  bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i, \u273 \u7875  b\u7885 n h\u7885  bi\u7871 t \u273 i\u7873 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297  qu\u7843  nhi\'ean qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t s\u7907  \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n l\'e0 c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c hay c\u7911 a th\u7907  s\u259 n, \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7845 n ch\u7881 nh khi\u7871 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  kinh s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7889 n ng\'e0y du l\u7883 ch Sydney trong k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi li\u7873 n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u7903  c\'f9ng h\u7855 n. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i v\u7915 a \u273 \'fang l\'fac h\u7855 n m\u432 \u7907 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t c\u259 n nh\'e0 \u273 \u7875  kh\'f4ng c\u7911 a b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, b\u7843 o Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7911 y kh\'e1ch s\u7841 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7863 t, d\u7885 n qua \u7903  chung v\u7899 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean thu\uc0\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng h\u7887 i l\'e0 b\u7841 n n\'e0o, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\u361 ng l\'e0 th\u7907  s\u259 n kh\'f4ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi li\u7873 n thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i c\u361 ng l\'e0 th\u7907  s\u259 n, b\u7883  ph\'e1i \u273 i \'c2u Ch\'e2u \u273 i c\'f4ng t\'e1c r\u7891 i, nh\'e0 \u7903  \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u273 \u7875  tr\u7889 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nghi ng\u7901  g\'ec, tho\'e1ng t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7871 n c\u7843 nh s\'e1t qu\u7889 c t\u7871 , c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n kia c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 m\u7897 t th\u7907  s\u259 n l\u7907 i h\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\'e0y \uc0\u273 \u7847 u hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i th\u259 m th\'fa nh\u7919 ng c\u7843 nh \u273 \u7865 p n\u7893 i ti\u7871 ng \u7903  Sydney, c\u361 ng th\u7917  t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c nh\'e0 h\'e0ng n\u7893 i danh, b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n ng\'e0y cu\u7889 i. V\'e9 m\'e1y bay Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7863 t l\'e0 chi\u7873 u h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 n\u259 m gi\u7901  quay v\u7873  Sophus, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi sau khi bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7863 t chuy\u7871 n bay \u273 \'f3 \u273 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u ph\u7843 i v\u7873  b\u7857 ng m\'e1y bay, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng s\u7855 p x\u7871 p h\'e0nh tr\'ecnh qu\'e1 d\'e0y, d\u7921  \u273 \u7883 nh bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng sau khi ng\u7911  d\u7853 y s\u7869  \u273 i d\u7841 o khu v\u7921 c xung quanh, \u259 n tr\u432 a xong th\'ec \u273 i c\'f4ng vi\'ean Hyde Park v\'e0 nh\'e0 th\u7901  Th\'e1nh Mary. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe c\u7853 u k\u7875  ho\u7841 ch, t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i ch\u7881  lu\'f4n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7855 ng nghe, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng ph\u7909  h\u7885 a v\'e0i c\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m nay l\uc0\u7841 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7847 y m\'e2y, t\u7915  s\'e1ng s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 m\u432 a bay nh\u7887 , \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 a m\u432 a l\u7899 n d\u7847 n. Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'fa t\u7841 m v\'e0o m\u7897 t ti\u7879 m \u259 n ven \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7915 a \u259 n v\u7915 a \u273 \u7907 i m\u432 a ng\u7899 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng m\u432 a v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng, t\u7915 ng gi\u7885 t kh\u7869  r\u417 i tr\'ean th\'e2n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7845 t ch\u7845 p m\u432 a ph\'f9n \u273 i d\u7841 o trong c\'f4ng vi\'ean. Nh\'e0 th\u7901  v\'e0 c\'f4ng vi\'ean n\u7857 m hai b\'ean m\u7897 t con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  c\'f4ng vi\'ean b\'ean n\'e0y l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y t\'f2a nh\'e0 l\u7899 n mang phong c\'e1ch Gothic trang nghi\'eam d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7855 c tr\u7901 i \'e2m u b\'ean kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i s\'f3ng vai \u273 i trong c\'f4ng vi\'ean m\u7897 t h\u7891 i, l\'fac sau Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c gh\u7871  d\u432 \u7899 i th\'e2n c\'e2y, n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "T\'f4i h\u417 i m\u7879 t r\u7891 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7913 ng th\'fa v\u7899 i nh\'e0 th\u7901  l\u7855 m, mu\u7889 n ng\u7891 i ch\u7895  n\'e0y ngh\u7881  m\u7897 t l\'e1t. C\u7853 u \u273 i xem \u273 i, l\'fac n\'e0o ra th\'ec b\'e1o t\'f4i, t\'f4i ch\u7901  c\u7853 u \u7903  giao l\u7897 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tuy r\uc0\u7857 ng th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  n\'f3i b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\u7879 t l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875 , nh\u432 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c kia Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7889 ng \u7903  \'c2u Ch\'e2u, lo\u7841 i nh\'e0 th\u7901  ph\u432 \u417 ng T\'e2y n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y kh\u7855 p n\u417 i, nh\'e0 th\u7901  n\u7893 i danh h\u417 n c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p kh\'f4ng \'edt, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c \u273 i th\u259 m quan nh\'e0 th\u7901  th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  th\u7845 y h\u7913 ng th\'fa. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7921 c k\'ec th\u7845 u hi\u7875 u g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  \u273 \'fang l\'e0 l\'fac s\u7855 p x\u7871 p h\'e0nh tr\'ecnh m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 s\u417  s\'f3t, kh\'f4ng t\'ednh \u273 \u7871 n \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng ra nh\'ecn th\u7901 i gian, n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, em s\u7869  \u273 i xem qua m\u7897 t v\'f2ng, t\u7889 i \u273 a m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m ph\'fat l\'e0 ra."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u ch\u7841 y \u273 i, du\u7895 i tay tr\'e1i ch\u7889 ng c\u7857 m nh\'ecn b\'f3ng l\u432 ng c\u7853 u, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  c\u361 ng may, Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  k\u7871 t h\'f4n v\u7899 i h\u7855 n \u7903  nh\'e0 th\u7901 . N\u7871 u \'e1i nh\'e2n mu\u7889 n h\u7855 n c\u7917  h\'e0nh h\'f4n l\u7877  \u7903  nh\'e0 th\u7901 , ch\u7855 c h\u7855 n s\u7869  \u273 i\'ean m\u7845 t, h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\'e0 t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i x\'e2y m\u7897 t t\'f2a nh\'e0 th\u7901  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c t\u7841 m th\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i Ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t, nh\'e0 th\u7901  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\'ean trong r\u7845 t y\'ean t\u297 nh, h\'e0ng gh\u7871  ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a v\'e0 hai b\'ean c\'f3 v\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang y\'ean l\u7863 ng c\u7847 u nguy\u7879 n ho\u7863 c th\'ec th\u7847 m \u273 \u7885 c kinh. M\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7863 c trang ph\u7909 c gi\'e1o s\u297  \u273 ang ph\'e1t c\u7889 c u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c cho m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c t\u432 \u7907 ng Th\'e1nh M\u7851 u \u273 \u7889 t n\u7871 n, \'e1nh n\u7871 n lay \u273 \u7897 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng qu\'e1 l\u7899 n, y\'ean \u7855 ng \u273 i d\u7885 c theo v\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng, xem x\'e9t n\'e9t kh\u7855 c tr\'ean v\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0 c\u7917 a s\u7893  th\u7911 y tinh m\'e0u s\u7855 c r\u7921 c r\u7905 . C\u7853 u \u273 i v\'e0o c\u7917 a t\u7915  tr\'e1i, v\'f2ng m\u7897 t v\'f2ng, l\'fac \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n t\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean ph\u7843 i th\'ec l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng ra nh\'ecn th\u7917 , \u273 \'e3 qua m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m ph\'fat, c\u7853 u n\'ean \u273 i ra t\'ecm Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e1t n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, \u273 \u432 a cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c: "\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c th\'e1nh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m ph\'e9p."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  kh\u7869  n\'f3i, v\u7869  h\'ecnh th\u7853 p t\u7921  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c: "Nguy\u7879 n Ch\'faa lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i l\'fang t\'fang, nh\u7853 n n\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3i "C\u7843 m \u417 n", suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m, c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u m\u7845 y l\u7877  ti\u7871 t t\'f4n gi\'e1o n\'e0y l\u7855 m, ch\u7881  khi \u273 i ch\'f9a m\u7899 i b\u7855 t ch\u432 \u7899 c ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c ch\u7855 p tay tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c ni\u7879 m A di \u273 \'e0 ph\u7853 t, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'fac n\'e0y ph\u7843 i l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng th\u7845 t l\u7877 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng thi\u7879 n \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, b\u432 ng khay r\u7901 i \u273 i ng\u432 \u7907 c h\u432 \u7899 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t h\u417 i u\u7889 ng h\u7871 t n\u432 \u7899 c trong c\u7889 c, \u273 \u7883 nh sau khi ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y th\'ec t\'ecm th\'f9ng r\'e1c v\u7913 t, nh\u432 ng v\u7915 a \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai b\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7907 t c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7897 t c\u417 n \u273 au nh\'f3i trong ng\u7921 c, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i tim \u273 \u7853 p nhanh b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, li\'ean t\u7909 c kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  s\u7855 p b\u7853 t ra kh\u7887 i ng\u7921 c. C\u7853 u che ng\u7921 c tr\'e1i, d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i, tim \u273 \u7853 p li\'ean h\u7891 i khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 \u7843 o gi\'e1c trong ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh m\u7885 c th\'eam m\u7897 t qu\u7843  tim\'97\'97 kh\'f4ng, l\'e0 c\'f3 v\'f4 s\u7889  tr\'e1i tim \u273 ang \u273 \u7853 p trong ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7889 ng tay tr\'e1i l\'ean v\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng, \'fd th\u7913 c d\u7847 n d\u7847 n m\u417  h\u7891 , c\u417  th\u7875  c\u361 ng c\'e0ng th\'eam v\'f4 l\u7921 c, kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 d\u7921 a v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng tu\u7897 t xu\u7889 ng. C\u7853 u th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e1t n\u432 \u7899 c th\'e1nh s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t bu\'f4ng khay, kh\u7849 n tr\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, mi\u7879 ng h\'f4 c\'e2u g\'ec \u273 \'f3, mu\u7889 n n\'e2ng c\u7853 u d\u7853 y...\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7841 i n\'e3o Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c x\u7917  l\'fd th\'eam th\'f4ng tin. Tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac ho\'e0n to\'e0n m\u7845 t \'fd th\u7913 c, h\'ecnh \u7843 nh cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y l\'e0 m\u7897 t nam nh\'e2n m\u7863 c \'e1o cho\'e0ng \u273 en \u273 i v\'e0o t\u7915  h\u432 \u7899 ng c\u7917 a ng\u432 \u7907 c s\'e1ng \'97\'97m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n d\'e0i \u273 en, \'e1o cho\'e0ng g\u7885 n gh\u7869 , c\u7847 n c\u7893  tr\u7855 ng x\'e1m thon d\'e0i, t\'f4n l\'ean m\'e0u m\'f4i \u273 \u7887  th\u7851 m, \'e1nh m\u7855 t s\'e2u \u273 en... Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915  d\u432 \u7899 i nh\'ecn l\'ean nam nh\'e2n, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng n\'e2ng tay v\u7899 i v\u7873  ph\'eda h\u7855 n, trong l\'f2ng g\u7885 i l\u7899 n t\'ean \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng...\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p..." C\u7853 u m\u7845 p m\'e1y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ch\u7919 , cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\'e1nh tay v\'f4 l\u7921 c bu\'f4ng xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh, hai m\u7855 t nh\u7855 m l\u7841 i. \u272 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7913 c l\u7879 ch sang vai tr\'e1i, l\u7897  ra ph\u7847 n c\u7893  b\'ean ph\u7843 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n \uc0\u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n, c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean r\u7901 i \u273 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n khi th\'e2n \u7843 nh c\u7853 u ho\'e0n to\'e0n bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u, ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e1t n\u432 \u7899 c th\'e1nh m\u7899 i l\u7845 y l\u7841 i tinh th\u7847 n. \'d4ng nh\'ecn quanh m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, n\'e9t m\u7863 t l\u7897  ra ch\'fat nghi ho\u7863 c: ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c? Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh b\u7883  ng\u7845 t sao? M\'ecnh c\'f2n \u273 ang \u273 \u7883 nh g\u7885 i c\u7845 p c\u7913 u m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, \u273 ang mu\u7889 n c\u7845 t b\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i kh\u7887 i, \'e1nh m\u7855 t d\u7901 i xu\u7889 ng l\u7841 i tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c c\u7889 c gi\u7845 y m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng r\u7895 ng \u273 \'e3 qua s\u7917  d\u7909 ng, gi\u7889 ng h\u7879 t nh\u7919 ng chi\u7871 c c\u7889 c kh\'e1c trong khay c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Sophus, trang vi\'ean Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey nh\'ecn Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \'f4m nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \u273 ang h\'f4n m\'ea v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 i l\'ean ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  tr\'ean l\u7847 u hai, trong l\'f2ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i kinh ng\u7841 c. Theo \'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 ang \u273 i h\u432 \u7903 ng tu\u7847 n tr\u259 ng m\u7853 t nh\u7887  sao? Th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i... ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7845 t t\u7881 nh? \u272 i\u7879 n h\u7841  \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m g\'ec r\u7891 i?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng theo sau Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i l\'ean l\u7847 u hai \u273 \u7875  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n t\'f9y th\u7901 i ra l\u7879 nh. Qu\u7843 n gia ti\'ean sinh \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  th\'ec d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'f3i: "Th\u7913  cho ta nhi\u7873 u l\u7901 i, \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng l\'fac n\'e0y l\'e0 sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng sofa, ti\u7879 n tay c\u7903 i \'e1o cho\'e0ng \u273 ang m\u7863 c n\'e9m qua m\u7897 t b\'ean gh\u7871 , ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng c\u7841 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u c\u7903 i n\'fat tay \'e1o tr\'e1i , v\u7915 a c\u7903 i v\u7915 a kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "H\u7855 n u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c th\'e1nh \u7903  nh\'e0 th\u7901 , th\'e1nh l\u7921 c trong n\u432 \u7899 c th\'e1nh c\'f4ng k\'edch m\'e1u d\u7851 n tr\u432 \u7899 c kia ta \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i trong c\u417  th\u7875  h\u7855 n, c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i n\'ean ng\u7845 t \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7903 i n\'fat tay \'e1o xong Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng k\'e9o \u7889 ng tay \'e1o l\'ean, \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y l\u7845 y chi\u7871 c dao b\u7841 c tr\'ean b\'e0n s\'e1ch, r\u7845 t nhanh c\u7855 t m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'ean c\u7893  tay tr\'e1i\'97\'97 m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i nhanh ch\'f3ng ch\u7843 y ra t\u7915  mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng. H\u7855 n \u273 \u432 a m\'e1u ch\u7843 y \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean mi\u7879 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng d\u7895 : "Ngoan, u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat s\u7869  kh\'f4ng kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Grey, n\'e9t m\u7863 t trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t t\u7915  d\u7895  d\'e0nh kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c th\'e0nh b\'ecnh t\u297 nh: "\u7902  \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng c\'f2n vi\u7879 c g\'ec n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e1u t\uc0\u432 \u417 i ch\u7843 y ra t\u7915  mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ean c\u7893  tay h\u7855 n mang theo h\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  h\u7855 c \'e1m c\u7921 c k\u7923  m\'ea ng\u432 \u7901 i. Ng\u432 \u7901 i kia gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  h\u7845 p d\u7851 n, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n t\u7915  trong h\'f4n m\'ea t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u trong hai m\u7855 t v\u7851 n l\'e0 s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 t\u7881 nh t\u7881 nh m\'ea m\'ea, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean \'fd th\u7913 c v\u7851 n ch\u432 a thanh t\u7881 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  t\u7921  \u273 \u432 a m\'f4i t\u7899 i c\u7893  tay Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u v\u7851 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 t\u7915 ng ch\'fat, th\u259 m d\'f2 m\'e0 li\u7871 m m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i ch\u7843 y ra, nh\u432 ng r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  th\'e0nh kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911 , ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng d\'f9ng hai tay \'f4m l\u7845 y c\'e1nh tay \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u tham lam m\'e0 h\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c dung t\'fang vu\u7889 t t\'f3c c\u7853 u, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t th\'e2m tr\u7847 m s\'e2u kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e1y, l\'fac n\'e0y d\u7915 ng tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang h\'fat m\'e1u h\u7855 n, c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u trong m\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i g\u7847 n nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'e0n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7891 ng t\u7917  m\'e0u x\'e1m c\u7911 a Grey b\u7903 i v\'ec s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t m\'e0 ph\'f3ng \u273 \u7841 i, th\u7845 y th\u7871  nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'f3i: "M\'e1u ng\'e0i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e1u l\'e0 ngu\uc0\u7891 n g\u7889 c s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, l\'e0 th\u7913  quan tr\u7885 ng nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a m\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. M\'e1u Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer qu\'fd gi\'e1 c\u7905  n\'e0o, \u7849 n ch\u7913 a ngu\u7891 n s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh l\u7899 n c\u7905  n\'e0o... \'d4ng ngay c\u7843  ngh\u297  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ngh\u297 .\cb1 \
