\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \'f4m nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i tham lam kia t\u7915  sofa t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i nh\u7887  h\u7865 p l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng song song v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o l\'f2ng, v\u7851 n dung t\'fang nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 d\'e2ng l\'ean c\u7893  tay m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'e9t m\uc0\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 d\'e3n ra r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, kh\'f4ng c\'f2n v\u7897 i v\'e0ng kh\'e1t c\u7847 u m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c. C\u7853 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  h\'fat m\u7887 i, l\u7841 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \'f4m l\u7845 y c\'e1nh tay li\u7871 m mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng t\u7915 ng ch\'fat t\u7915 ng ch\'fat, hai m\u7855 t c\u361 ng d\u7847 n kh\'e9p k\'edn. Qua h\u7891 i l\'e2u, c\u7853 u t\u7915  t\u7915  an t\u297 nh l\u7841 i trong s\u7921  v\u7895  v\u7873  tr\u7845 n an c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, coi c\'e1nh tay h\u7855 n nh\u432  b\u7843 o b\u7889 i m\'e0 \'f4m ch\u7863 t, \'e1p d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7863 t r\u7891 i ng\u7911  m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer t\u7909  s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh t\u7841 i mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng, v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7843 y m\'e1u r\u7845 t nhanh kh\'e9p l\u7841 i, tr\u417 n nh\u7861 n, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ra d\u7845 u v\u7871 t l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c b\u7883  r\u7841 ch. H\u7855 n kh\'f4ng n\u7905  r\'fat c\'e1nh tay ra, li\u7873 n duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u \'f4m g\u7889 i ng\u7911 , \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \u273 \u432 a tay x\u7889 c ch\u259 n ph\u7911  l\'ean hai ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i v\'ec qu\'e1 m\u7913 c nh\'e0m ch\'e1n ho\u7863 c c\u226 \u768 n ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c m\'e0 c\u7889  \'fd ng\u7911 , th\u7853 t ra h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ng\u7911 . M\'e0 gi\u7901  kh\u7855 c n\'e0y trong ph\'f2ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n y\'ean t\u297 nh, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng l\'f2 s\u432 \u7903 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng ch\'e1y l\'e1ch t\'e1ch, b\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed r\u7891 i v\u7843 i nhung \u273 \u7873 u \u7845 m \'e1p, ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c c\u361 ng m\u7873 m m\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n xa r\u7901 i m\'e0 \'f4m tay h\u7855 n; th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng trong m\u7897 ng nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng r\u7847 m r\'ec hai ti\u7871 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  ai \u7903  trong m\u7897 ng khi d\u7877  l\'e0m m\u7845 t h\u7913 ng; c\'f3 khi cong kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng im \u7855 ng c\u432 \u7901 i, v\'f4 th\u7913 c in m\'f4i l\'ean c\'e1nh tay h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u qu\'e1 t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 , ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c. M\'e0 h\u7855 n c\u361 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  ng\u7911  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, nh\u432  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  l\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e1c \u7903  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7855 c tr\u7901 i d\u7847 n t\u7889 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 l\'f2 s\u432 \u7903 i gian ngo\'e0i ph\'e1t ra \'e1nh l\u7917 a m\'e0u v\u7887  qu\'fdt, c\u259 n ph\'f2ng t\u7889 i \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c. Trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\u7903  m\u7855 t, b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng. K\u7923  th\u7853 t trong b\'f3ng \u273 \'eam h\u7855 n v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\u7885 i th\u7913 , nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \'f4m c\'e1nh tay h\u7855 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng r\u7847 m r\'ec k\'eau, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng chui v\'e0o v\'e0o trong l\'f2ng h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e8n gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0u cam s\'e1ng l\'ean, \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n \u7845 m \'e1p l\u7853 p t\u7913 c bao ph\u7911  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 . Qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\u7897  ra n\'e9t m\u7863 t \'f4n nhu, k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng vu\u7889 t ve m\'e1 c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean, b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, t\u7881 nh t\u7881 nh, l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? Kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\u7853 t d\'e0i m\u7903  m\u7855 t, \'fd th\u7913 c t\u7915  trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i d\u7847 n t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'ea mang m\'e0 nh\'ecn l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang \'f4m m\'ecnh \'97\'97 m\u7885 i th\u7913  t\u7889 i \u273 en, m\u417  m\u417  h\u7891  h\u7891 , c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y r\'f5.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7855 t nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y, c\'e1c gi\'e1c quan v\'e0 tr\'ed nh\u7899  li\u7873 n tr\u7903  n\'ean \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t nh\u7841 y. \u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng cho c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\'f4 c\'f9ng quen thu\u7897 c, c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\u7899  r\'f5 b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c m\u7863 c \'fd h\'fat m\'e1u l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean do d\uc0\u7921  m\u7897 t l\'e1t, th\u259 m d\'f2 h\u7887 i: "Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c hai gi\'e2y, thanh \'e2m l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m \u273 \'e1p: "L\'e0 ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u361 ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, \'e1nh m\u7855 t v\'f4 th\u7847 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  m\'f9. H\u7855 n \u273 \u432 a tay l\'ean tr\'e1n c\u7853 u ki\u7875 m tra th\u7917 \'97\'97 m\'e1u d\u7851 n h\u7855 n \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i trong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u v\'e0 m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i l\'fac sau h\u7855 n cho c\u7853 u h\'fat \u273 ang thi\'eau \u273 \u7889 t th\'e1nh l\u7921 c c\'f2n s\'f3t l\u7841 i trong c\u417  th\u7875 , th\'e1nh l\u7921 c v\u7851 n \u273 ang ngoan c\u7889  m\'e0 li\u7873 u ch\u7871 t ph\u7843 n kh\'e1ng, hai ngu\u7891 n l\u7921 c \u273 \u7889 i ch\u7885 i \u273 \'e8 l\'ean d\'e2y th\u7847 n kinh th\u7883  gi\'e1c trong c\u417  th\u7875 , \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n s\'e1ng mai khi th\'e1nh l\u7921 c \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n b\u7883  xu\u7845 t ra th\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f2n g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng lo n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bi\uc0\u7871 t r\'f5 nguy\'ean nh\'e2n h\u7855 n li\u7873 n y\'ean t\'e2m. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  ma xui qu\u7927  khi\u7871 n th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 A Di\'ean hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, tr\'e1i l\u7841 i l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n ra h\u7855 n l\'e0 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer... Ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7841 m th\u7901 i \u273 \u7893 i vai v\u7853 y. Song c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec, d\'f9 sao l\'e0m vi\u7879 c n\'e0y h\u7855 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 quen.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao t\'f4i l\uc0\u7841 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y?" Qu\u7843  nhi\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean hi\u7879 n ra v\'e0i ph\u7847 n lo s\u7907  nghi ho\u7863 c b\u7845 t an, "... B\u7841 n t\'f4i \u273 \'e2u?" L\'fac \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 h\u7865 n g\u7863 p nhau ngo\'e0i nh\'e0 th\u7901 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  \u273 i t\'ecm c\u7853 u, h\u417 n n\u7919 a b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y tr\u432 \u7899 c khi ng\u7845 t \u273 i ... r\'f5 r\'e0ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 b\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  c\u7853 u l\u7841 i \u273 ang ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7841 n ng\u432 \u417 i?" Thanh \'e2m Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng nh\'e0n nh\'e3 nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c, "Ng\u432 \u417 i n\'f3i t\'ean th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  kia? L\'e0 h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh \uc0\u7845 y \u273 \u432 a t\'f4i t\u7899 i? T\u7841 i sao?" Gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ph\u7847 n gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh, c\'f2n tho\'e1ng ch\'fat kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tin.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c kia ta \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i m\'e1u d\u7851 n trong c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i, nh\u432  v\u7853 y b\u7845 t c\u7913  l\'fac n\'e0o ta \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  n\u7855 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'e0nh tung c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i, nh\u432 ng h\'f4m nay \u7903  nh\'e0 th\u7901  ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 \'e3 u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c th\'e1nh, th\'e1nh l\u7921 c \u7849 n trong n\u432 \u7899 c th\'e1nh c\'f4ng k\'edch m\'e1u d\u7851 n trong c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i, mu\u7889 n \'e9p n\'f3 ra, c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'ean ng\u7845 t \u273 i. \u272 \'f3 l\'e0 m\'e1u d\u7851 n c\u7911 a ta, th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  kia kh\'f4ng c\u7913 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u417 i, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ph\u7843 i \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 "M\'e1u d\uc0\u7851 n?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\'c0, m\uc0\u7897 t th\u7911  thu\u7853 t nh\u7887  th\'f4i. N\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ng\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh ch\u7841 y m\u7845 t th\'ec l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o? Ta bi\u7871 t \u273 i \u273 \'e2u t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e2y?" Trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  mang ch\'fat ti\u7871 u \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y ho\'e0n th\'e0nh ba m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh, ng\'e0i s\u7869  lo\u7841 i n\'f3 \u273 i ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "... \uc0\u7914 m." Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng t\u7887  \'fd ki\u7871 n, th\u7901  \u417  \u273 \'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i cho l\'e0 h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  sau khi r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y ph\u7843 i \u273 i t\'ecm Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7887 i l\u7841 i cho r\'f5 r\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7841 ch m\'e1u trong c\u417  th\u7875  \u273 \u7853 p th\'ecnh th\u7883 ch, huy\u234 \u769 t di\u803 ch nh\u432  s\'f4i l\'ean, to\'e0n th\'e2n s\'f4i tr\'e0o c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'f3ng r\u7921 c kh\'f3 nh\u7883 n. M\'e1u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c cho c\u7853 u u\u7889 ng \u273 ang thi\'eau \u273 \u7889 t th\'e1nh l\u7921 c c\'f2n s\'f3t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  cho l\'e0 di ch\u7913 ng h\'f4n m\'ea, m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, ch\u7881  t\'f2 m\'f2 h\u7887 i: "Ng\'e0i, ng\'e0i c\u7913 u t\'f4i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec, " Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer kh\u7869  vu\u7889 t ve g\'e1y c\u7853 u, thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i, "Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m th\'e1nh l\u7921 c v\'e0 m\'e1u d\u7851 n trong c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i ngang s\u7913 c, ch\'fang s\u7869  c\'f4ng k\'edch \u273 \u7875  lo\u7841 i tr\u7915  m\'e1u d\u7851 n, ng\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i n\'ean ng\u7845 t \u273 i, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u417  th\u7875  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  t\u7893 n h\u7841 i. Ch\u7881  c\u7847 n cho ng\u432 \u417 i u\u7889 ng m\'e1u ta, d\'f9ng s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh l\u7899 n h\u417 n \'e1p ch\u7871  th\'e1nh l\u7921 c. C\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i s\u7869  y\'ean tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, d\u297  nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 "... C\'e1m \uc0\u417 n ng\'e0i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai th\u7845 p \u273 \u7847 u, l\'fang t\'fang n\'f3i. N\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 cho c\u7853 u u\u7889 ng m\'e1u h\u7855 n? C\u7853 u u\u7889 ng m\'e1u Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer? \'dd th\u7913 c b\u7903 i suy ngh\u297  n\'e0y m\'e0 c\'e0ng th\'eam xao \u273 \u7897 ng, ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u khao kh\'e1t huy\u234 \u769 t di\u803 ch c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u432 \u7899 c v\u7885 ng c\u7911 a c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u \u273 ang lo l\u7855 ng m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c: "T\'f4i u\u7889 ng m\'e1u ng\'e0i? S\u7869  kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 ? V\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u g\'ec \u273 \'f3..." D\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i ch\u7881  c\u7847 n u\u7889 ng m\'e1u c\u7911 a ch\'fang, s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi l\uc0\u7901 i ra kh\u7887 i mi\u7879 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7887 i v\u7853 y c\'f3 ph\u7847 n th\u7845 t l\u7877 , c\'e0ng th\'eam ng\u432 \u7907 ng m\'e0 c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u, nh\u432 ng theo \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c n\'e0y ph\u7847 n g\'e1y m\u7873 m m\u7841 i d\u432 \u7899 i b\'e0n tay Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7841 i c\'e0ng l\u7897  ra th\'eam.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  l\u7901 i c\u7853 u n\'f3i l\'e0m h\'e0i l\'f2ng, nh\'e9o nh\'e9o ph\u7847 n th\u7883 t m\u7873 m tr\'ean g\'e1y c\u7853 u, kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, t\'e2m t\'ecnh r\u7845 t t\u7889 t m\'e0 gi\u7843 i th\'edch: "Sao c\'f3 th\u7875 . Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m S\u417  \u7910 ng, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c s\u7869  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7911 a nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n S\u417  \u7910 ng cho \u273 \u7871 n khi \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec m\u7845 t m\'e1u qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u m\'e0 g\u7847 n ch\u7871 t, t\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng t\u7855 t th\u7903  ph\u7843 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c cho u\u7889 ng m\'e1u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. Tuy nhi\'ean S\u417  \u7910 ng c\u361 ng c\'f3 t\u7927  l\u7879  th\u7845 t b\u7841 i r\u7845 t l\u7899 n, nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n S\u417  \u7910 ng r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  t\u7917  vong ngay khi \u273 \'f3, ho\u7863 c bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh k\u7867  m\u7845 t tr\'ed kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'f3 \'fd th\u7913 c, ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t tr\u7889 n trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i s\u259 n gi\u7871 t nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i h\'fat m\'e1u, sau \u273 \'f3 b\u7883  th\u7907  s\u259 n ti\'eau di\u7879 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, h\'e0m r\u259 ng nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u: "... Tuy r\u7857 ng ta \u273 \'e3 h\'fat m\'e1u ng\u432 \u417 i nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n, nh\u432 ng c\'f3 l\u7847 n n\'e0o \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i g\u7847 n ch\u7871 t hay kh\'f4ng? Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i v\u7915 a h\'fat hai l\u7847 n \u273 \'e3 cho ng\u432 \u417 i n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c hay sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ti\uc0\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i v\'f4 l\u432 \u417 ng t\'e2m " h\u7855 n th\'ec th\u7847 m, "M\u7895 i l\u7847 n ta h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng n\u7905  h\'fat nhi\u7873 u nh\u432  ng\u432 \u417 i h\'fat m\'e1u ta. Ng\u432 \u417 i th\'ec gi\u7887 i l\u7855 m, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u259 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u bu\'f4ng ra." H\u7855 n o\'e1n tr\'e1ch, trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 \'fd o\'e1n gi\u7853 n, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  n\u7871 u b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng u\u7889 ng m\'e1u nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u361 ng s\u7869  vui v\u7867  ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i n\'f3ng l\'ean, ph\'e1t nhi\u7879 t, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\'f4m nay th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer c\'e0ng th\'eam k\u7923  qu\'e1i, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n l\u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'f3i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 th\u7853 t. K\u7923  d\u7883  nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m nghe Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer than c\u7853 u tham lam h\'fat m\'e1u h\u7855 n, c\u7893  h\u7885 ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'e1t, n\'f3ng r\u7921 c, nh\u432  \u273 ang \u273 \'f3n ch\u7901  m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i ch\u7845 t l\u7887 ng n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7871 n th\u7887 a m\'e3n n\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f2n mu\uc0\u7889 n u\u7889 ng. Mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng m\'e1u c\u7911 a h\u7855 n. M\'e1u c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng k\'ecm \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t. Sau khi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7853 n ra l\u7841 i b\u7883  \'fd ngh\u297  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'e0m cho c\'e0ng th\'eam ho\u7843 ng s\u7907  \'97\'97r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u7853 u \u273 ang kh\'e1t v\u7885 ng m\'e1u Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Qu\u7927 . C\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u \u273 i\'ean r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c v\u7851 n lu\'f4n ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn n\'e9t m\u7863 t c\u7853 u, th\u7845 y v\u7853 y con m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i t\u7889 i l\u7841 i \'97\'97t\u7915  l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c cho c\u7853 u u\u7889 ng m\'e1u \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 qua s\'e1u b\u7843 y gi\u7901 , c\'f3 l\u7869  m\'e1u \u273 \'e3 ti\'eau hao kh\'f4ng \'edt, cho n\'ean A Di\'ean l\u7841 i mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng m\'e1u sao? N\u7871 u A Di\'ean mu\u7889 n, s\u7869  h\u7887 i m\'ecnh ch\u7913 ? S\u7869  c\u7847 u m\'ecnh ch\u7913 ? N\u7871 u m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng th\u7887 a m\'e3n, li\u7879 u A Di\'ean s\u7869  l\'e0m n\u361 ng v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, hay l\'e0 s\u7869  ph\'e1t gi\u7853 n v\u7899 i m\'ecnh?\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 suy ngh\u297  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng \u273 u\'f4i nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \'e3 khi\u7871 n h\u7855 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau, th\u7853 m ch\'ed tho\'e1ng ch\'fat ch\u7901  mong, \'e1nh m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u nhu h\'f2a m\'e0 mang theo \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y n\'e9t m\u7863 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'fd ngh\u297  c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t \'fd ni\u7879 m, mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng m\'e1u, mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng m\'e1u, mu\u7889 n m\'e1u Emmer... B\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u417  th\u7875  h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i h\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  h\u7855 c \'e1m th\u417 m ng\u7885 t kia, tuy r\u7857 ng ch\'ednh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nh\u7899  t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u kh\u7869  run, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u273 \u7845 u tranh v\u7899 i ham mu\u7889 n h\'fat m\'e1u. Tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 ang x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n tr\u7847 m m\'ea trong c\'e1m d\u7895  m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i c\u7911 a qu\'e1i v\u7853 t \'97\'97 sao c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng m\'e1u m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y qu\'e1 k\'ec qu\'e1i. C\u7853 u d\u7889 c s\u7913 c k\'e9o \'fd th\u7913 c v\'e0 l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd t\u7915  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Emmer tr\u7903  v\u7873 , d\u7889 c s\u7913 c t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng m\'f9i v\u7883  m\'e1u v\u7883 t m\'e1u heo trong n\u7891 i l\u7849 u... Th\u7871  nh\u432 ng v\'f4 d\u7909 ng, c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 kh\'e1t v\u7885 ng Emmer, kh\'e1t v\u7885 ng m\'e1u c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ng\u7891 i qu\u7923  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c Emmer, h\u7889 c m\u7855 t b\u7903 i \u273 \u7845 u tranh v\u7899 i ham mu\u7889 n h\'fat m\'e1u m\'e0 \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean l\'f3ng l\'e1nh \u432 \u7899 t n\u432 \u7899 c, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7845 t m\'e3n v\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e1u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\'e0m c\u7853 u kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i ch\u7843 y n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t sinh l\'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c kh\'f4ng kh\u7855 c ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n m\'e0 than nh\u7865  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, hai tay \u273 \'e8 l\'ean vai Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7855 n l\'ean g\'e1y h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
