\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7855 n l\'ean s\u432 \u7901 n c\u7893  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. Nh\u432 ng b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m d\'f9ng s\u7913 c qu\'e1 m\u7841 nh, nhay t\u7899 i nhay lui, thay \u273 \u7893 i m\u7845 y g\'f3c \u273 \u7897 , c\u361 ng ch\u7881  in l\u7841 i m\u7897 t d\u7845 u r\u259 ng m\u7901  m\u7901 , \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng \u7849 m \u432 \u7899 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  th\u7921 c nh\u432  c\'fan con ch\u432 a m\u7885 c r\u259 ng \u273 \'f9a ngh\u7883 ch. Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 \'f4m l\u7845 y c\u7853 u, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "Ng\u432 \u417 i l\'e0 \u273 ang ch\u417 i v\u7899 i ta sao? L\'e0 \u273 ang h\'f4n ta sao? Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7909 t ch\'ed m\'e0 thu mi\u7879 ng v\u7873 , m\'ea mang m\u7903  to \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u \u273 en v\'f4 th\u7847 n "Nh\'ecn" Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, s\u7901  t\'ecm tay tr\'e1i \u273 ang \u273 \u7905  sau l\u432 ng m\'ecnh, k\'e9o xu\u7889 ng k\u7873  v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng c\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i xu\u7889 ng c\u7893  tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7855 n tay c\'f2n kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng s\u7913 c b\u7857 ng c\u7855 n c\u7893 , c\u7853 u mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng th\u7917  m\u7845 y l\u7847 n, ngay c\u7843  d\u7845 u r\u259 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng th\'eam m\uc0\u7901  m\u7883 t, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'f3ng ch\'e1y do m\'e1u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c v\'e0 th\'e1nh l\u7921 c \u273 \u7889 i ch\u7885 i nhau trong c\u417  th\u7875  thi\'eau c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n mu\u7889 n kh\'f3c, trong ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7921 c k\u7923  kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\'ecm ra c\'e1ch gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t. \'dd th\u7913 c \u273 \'e3 d\u7847 n kh\'f4ng c\'f2n t\u7881 nh t\'e1o l\u7855 m, c\u7853 u theo b\u7843 n n\u259 ng d\u7921 a v\'e0o ng\u7921 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, li\u7873 u m\u7841 ng h\'fat l\u7845 y kh\'ed t\u7913 c c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, d\'f9ng ch\'fang gi\u7843 m b\u7899 t kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u trong ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\u7921 a trong ng\u7921 c qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, hai tay v\'f2ng l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n, ng\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t nh\'ecn \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, hai m\u7855 t tho\'e1ng h\u7891 ng, long lanh n\u432 \u7899 c nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, bi\u7875 u l\u7897  h\u7895 n t\u7841 p kh\'f3 nh\u7883 n, l\'ean \'e1n c\'f9ng c\u7847 u kh\u7849 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7921 c k\'ec \u7911 y khu\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \u432 a tay \u273 i\u7875 m m\u361 i c\u7853 u, c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4n m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, trong mi\u7879 ng th\'ec th\u7847 m: "\u272 \u7915 ng nh\'ecn ta nh\u432  v\u7853 y, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\u7841 i l\'e0 ta khi d\u7877  em, r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 em ng\u7889 c, ng\u432 \u7901 i ta cho c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng d\'e1m u\u7889 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'f5 r\'e0ng b\uc0\u7897  d\u7841 ng \'fd th\u7913 c m\u417  h\u7891 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i nh\u432  trong ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c nghe hi\u7875 u l\u7901 i h\u259 \u769 n n\'f3i, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, \'f4m eo h\u7855 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7915  h\u7915  hai ti\u7871 ng, n\'e9t m\u7863 t c\'e0ng th\'eam oan \u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\u7869  ch\u7885 c ch\u7885 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u: "C\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau. S\u7855 p kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'fd th\uc0\u7913 c m\u7901  m\u7883 t d\'f9ng m\u7863 t c\u7885  c\u7885  ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, l\'f4ng mi kh\u7869  \u273 \u7897 ng, trong mi\u7879 ng nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng l\u7849 m b\u7849 m: "Emmer, c\u7913 u t\'f4i. C\u7847 u ng\'e0i, t\'f4i \u273 \u7875  ng\'e0i u\u7889 ng m\'e1u t\'f4i. Ng\'e0i \u273 \u7915 ng m\u7863 c k\u7879  t\'f4i, l\'e0 t\'f4i sai r\u7891 i, v\u7873  sau m\'e1u c\u7911 a t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u cho ng\'e0i, chuy\u7879 n g\'ec t\'f4i c\u361 ng nghe theo ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe v\'e0o th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 v\u7915 a m\u7873 m v\u7915 a ngoan, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\'f2ng xao \u273 \u7897 ng kh\'f4ng th\'f4i, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'e0ng \'f4m ch\u7863 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, li\u7871 m li\u7871 m r\u259 ng. H\u7855 n th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n r\'f5 l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u273 ang t\u7881 nh t\'e1o hay kh\'f4ng, n\u7871 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i, sao c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 ang trong ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c m\'e0 bi\u7871 t nghe l\u7901 i nh\u432  th\u7871 , sao c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i ra nhi\u7873 u l\u7901 i l\'e0m h\u7855 n vui s\u432 \u7899 ng nh\u432  th\u7871 . Ngh\u297  v\u7853 y, t\'e2m tr\'ed h\u7855 n l\u7841 i nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bay xa, nh\u7899  t\u7899 i \u273 \'eam h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n n\'e0y, ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng m\'e0 b\'f2 d\u7853 y ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng d\'e2ng l\'ean n\u7909  h\'f4n \u7845 m \u7845 m m\u7873 m m\u7873 m, c\u7847 u h\u7855 n th\u432 \u417 ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'e0ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng kh\'e1ng c\u7921  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 l\'e0m h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o. Ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  ch\u7883 u th\'e0nh th\u7853 t m\'e0 ngoan ngo\'e3n theo h\u7855 n, lu\'f4n t\u7921  r\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i phi\u7873 n to\'e1i, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n h\u7855 n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u v\'f4 k\u7871  kh\u7843  thi, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  thu\u7853 n theo t\'e2m \'fd c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, th\u7887 a hi\u7879 p r\u7891 i l\u7841 i th\u7887 a hi\u7879 p, ch\u7881  s\u7907  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng vui, ch\u7881  s\u7907  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng v\u7915 a \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c \'f4m c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean \u273 i ra ph\'f2ng ngo\'e0i, l\u7845 y chi\u7871 c dao b\u7841 c tr\'ean b\'e0n s\'e1ch r\u7891 i l\u7841 i \'f4m v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \u273 \u7863 t c\u7853 u qua m\u7897 t b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, d\'e9m ch\u259 n c\u7849 n th\u7853 n, c\u7847 m dao r\u7841 ch c\u7893  tay m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  h\u7855 c \'e1m \u273 \u7871 n xa hoa c\u7911 a m\'e1u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c lan ra t\u7913  ph\'eda. Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n h\u7855 n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u432 a c\u7893  tay t\u7899 i, nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i ng\u7917 i th\u7845 y m\'f9i m\'e1u \u273 \'e3 nhanh ch\'f3ng b\'f2 t\u7915  ch\u259 n ra, ng\u7891 i qu\u7923  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n, hai tay n\'e2ng c\u7893  tay ch\u7843 y m\'e1u c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7845 t c\u7849 n th\u7853 n. Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u v\u432 \u417 n l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m li\u7871 m, l\u7841 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u ng\u7917 a m\u7863 t ngoan ngo\'e3n ch\u7901  \'fd c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7867  kh\'f4ng vui ho\u7863 c c\'f3 \'fd c\u7843 n tr\u7903  m\u7899 i v\'f9i \u273 \u7847 u m\u7863 c \'fd h\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u h\'fat \u273 \u7871 n vui s\u432 \u7899 ng. Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer d\'f9ng tay ph\u7843 i k\'e9o ch\u259 n ph\u7911  l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u, sau \u273 \'f3 vu\u7889 t ve \u273 \u7881 nh \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0 g\'e1y c\u7853 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng thu\u7853 n theo m\'e0 \u273 \'f3n nh\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean no b\uc0\u7909 ng r\u7891 i li\u7873 n \'f4m c\'e1nh tay h\u7855 n ng\u7911 . Qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u mu\u7889 n r\'fat tay v\u7873 , l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \'f4m r\u7845 t ch\u7863 t, ph\'e1t gi\'e1c h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n c\u432 \u7899 p v\u7873  c\'f2n ph\'e1t ra gi\u7885 ng m\u361 i b\u7845 t m\'e3n kh\'e1ng ngh\u7883  t\u7915  trong m\u7897 ng. Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\'e1ch n\'e0o, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean g\u7889 i \u273 \u7847 u, b\u7843 n th\'e2n th\'ec nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7857 m b\'ean c\u7841 nh, v\u432 \u417 n tay nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \'f4m \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao em \'f4m tay ta, ta \'f4m em, c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7845 t g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m sau, tr\uc0\u7901 i m\u7899 i t\u7901  m\u7901  s\'e1ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 t\u7881 nh. H\u7855 n ki\u7875 m tra th\u7917  t\'ecnh h\'ecnh c\u417  th\u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\'e1nh l\u7921 c \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  ti\'eau tr\u7915  h\u7871 t. H\u7855 n suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i r\'fat c\'e1nh tay t\'ea d\u7841 i ra, tr\u7903  m\'ecnh l\u7845 y m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c kh\u259 n l\u7909 a m\'e0u \u273 en t\u7915  trong ng\u259 n k\'e9o t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, kh\'f4ng y\'ean t\'e2m m\'e0 bu\u7897 c kh\u259 n che l\u7841 i m\u7855 t c\u7853 u\'97\'97 ai bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7875 u h\u7895 n \u273 \u7843 n nh\'e0 h\u7855 n s\u7869  t\u7881 nh l\'fac n\'e0o ch\u7913 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7859 ng l\u7869  g\u7841 t c\u7853 u l\'e0 n\u7857 m m\u417 ? Ch\u7881  s\u7907  g\u7841 t kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i. Hu\u7889 ng chi tuy\'ean d\'e2m gi\u7919 a ban ng\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t. . . Qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u li\u7871 m li\u7871 m r\u259 ng, th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng d\'e1m th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n n\u259 m ch\u7919  kia t\'e2m t\u432  kh\u7869  \u273 \u7897 ng \'97\'97 \u7915 m, d\'f9 sao \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\'e0 n\'f3i ban ng\'e0y m\u7899 i l\'e0 th\u7901 i gian \u273 i ng\u7911  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng,. . . Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  m\u7899 i t\u7881 nh, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1nh s\'e1ng h\u417 i y\u7871 u, nh\u432 ng c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y, tr\'ean m\u7855 t nh\u432  b\u7883  v\u7853 t g\'ec che, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\u7841 i r\u7845 t quen thu\u7897 c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 a thay s\u7901  s\u7901 , qu\u7843  nhi\'ean, l\'e0 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c kh\u259 n l\u7909 a \u273 en.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u7899  ra b\'e2y gi\u7901  m\'ecnh \u273 ang \u7903  ch\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i nh\u7899  t\u7899 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n ph\'e1t sinh \u273 \'eam qua \'97\'97 k\u7875  c\u7843  c\u7853 u \'f4m Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, kh\'f3c, l\'e0m n\u361 ng \u259 n v\u7841  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, n\'f3i l\u7901 i l\u7845 y l\'f2ng c\u7847 u h\u7855 n cho m\'ecnh u\u7889 ng m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t c\u7853 u tho\'e1ng c\'e1i n\'f3ng l\'ean, kh\'f4ng k\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 r\'ean m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng \'f4m m\'e1 tr\'e1i, suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\u7841 i n\'e2ng tay ph\u7843 i \'f4m m\'e1 ph\u7843 i. M\u7863 c d\'f9 trong nh\u7919 ng gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kia, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u vi\u7879 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n nh\'ecn, \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u l\u7901 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n nghe kh\'f4ng l\u7885 t m\'e0 m\u7895 i l\u7847 n nh\u7899  t\u7899 i \u273 \u7873 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y x\u7845 u h\u7893  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai bi\u7871 t, l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\'f9ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer t\'ednh ch\u7845 t ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'e1c nhau. Ch\'ednh m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  m\u7845 t m\u7863 t tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe th\uc0\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 ang \u273 i t\u7899 i, m\u7863 t c\u7853 u c\'e0ng \u273 \u7887  h\u417 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, b\u7845 t an m\'e0 si\u7871 t ga gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'fai th\u7845 p \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 c\'e1ch m\'ecnh r\u7845 t g\u7847 n: "Xin l\u7895 i, h\'f4m qua. . . \u273 \'e3 u\u7889 ng m\'e1u c\u7911 a ng\'e0i nhi\u7873 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u7853 u r\u7845 t k\u7923  v\u7885 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng qu\'ean h\u7871 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c c\u7853 u l\'e0m v\'e0 l\u7901 i c\u7853 u n\'f3i h\'f4m qua, nh\u432 ng hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean \u273 i\u7873 u n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\u7921 c t\u7871 , c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh m\'e0 gi\u7843  v\u7901  \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i t\u7921  an \u7911 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n r\u7857 ng \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \'e3 s\u7889 ng h\u417 n m\u7897 t ngh\'ecn n\u259 m m\'e0 n\'f3i th\'ec c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec m\'e0 ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y? C\u259 n b\u7843 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng coi vi\u7879 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng ngu xu\u7849 n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec to t\'e1t, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n t\u7921  t\'ecm phi\u7873 n n\'e3o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 ang ghim tr\'ean m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'e0ng th\'eam kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean, v\'ec mu\u7889 n x\'f3a b\u7887  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'fang t\'fang n\'e0y th\u7853 m ch\'ed qu\u7923  g\u7889 i b\u432 \u7899 c hai b\u432 \u7899 c v\u7873  ph\'eda Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, k\u7873  s\'e1t v\'e0o h\u7855 n r\u7891 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng n\'e2ng c\u7893  l\'ean, l\u7897  ra l\'e0n da m\u7887 ng y\u7871 u \u7899 t c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y m\u7841 ch m\'e1u m\'e0u xanh l\u7901  m\u7901 . C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u ngh\u297  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u \'fd c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'f3n tay l\uc0\u7841 nh l\u7869 o c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng vu\u7889 t ve: "Ta nh\u7899  h\'f4m qua ng\u432 \u417 i n\'f3i, v\u7873  sau m\'e1u c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7873 u cho ta h\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\'fai xu\u7889 ng, k\'e9o ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, r\u259 ng nh\u7885 n trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'e2m th\u7911 ng l\'e0n da m\u7873 m m\u7841 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o m\'e0 \u7845 m \'e1p, t\u432  v\u7883  c\u7911 a \'e1i nh\'e2n, tho\'e1ng nh\u432  c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c h\'f2a l\'e0m m\u7897 t th\u7875 . H\u7855 n th\u7887 a m\'e3n m\'e0 kh\'e9p \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en, sau m\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i r\'fat r\u259 ng ra, th\u7903  ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i th\u7853 t d\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n li\u7871 m l\'e1p d\u7845 u r\u259 ng v\'e0 mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ean c\u7847 n c\u7893 , c\u7889  t\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t d\u7845 u r\u259 ng b\u7883  r\u259 ng nanh c\u7855 n kh\'f4ng x\u7917  l\'fd. H\u7855 n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7899 i tay \u273 ang kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 run r\u7849 y , c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "Ti\u7875 u \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a ta, l\u7901 i ng\u432 \u417 i n\'f3i c\'f2n t\'ednh ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\uc0\u7885 c gi\u7853 n h\u7855 n, l\u7841 i ch\u417 i x\u7845 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n, trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n m\u417  h\u7891 , kh\'f4ng d\'e1m kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i m\'ecnh n\'f3i ra l\'fac v\'f4 th\u7913 c \u273 \'f3 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f3 ph\u7843 i l\'e0 l\u7901 i th\u7853 t l\'f2ng hay kh\'f4ng. . . B\'e8n quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7845 p l\u7917 ng \u273 \'e1p n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f4i: ". . . Hai th\'e1ng sau t\'f4i ph\u7843 i v\u7873  nh\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 \u273 \u7883 nh r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i ta? R\u259 ng nanh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ch\u432 a thu h\u7891 i l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a \u273 \'e2m xuy\'ean qua g\'e1y c\u7853 u, h\u7855 n nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\'ean ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng th\u7843  nh\u7865  \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c, l\u7841 i duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  ng\u7853 m m\'fat g\'e1y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng tha.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0. . . Ti\u7875 u h\u7895 n \u273 \u7843 n ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t n\'f3i d\u7889 i l\u7845 y l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
