\cb3 Cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u259 n tr\u432 a xong Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer b\u7843 o Grey \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u v\u7873 . L\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m b\'ecnh t\u297 nh gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  chuy\u7879 n g\'ec c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng x\u7843 y ra, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 c l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n ph\'e1t sinh h\'f4m qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t h\u417 i, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong l\'f2ng tr\u7889 ng v\u7855 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7845 t \u273 i th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3. C\u7853 u v\u7853 y m\'e0. . . c\'f3 ph\u7847 n mu\u7889 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u y\'eau c\u7847 u c\u7853 u \u7903  l\u7841 i nh\u432  m\u7845 y l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 d\'f9ng th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n \'e9p c\u7853 u l\u432 u l\u7841 i. C\u7853 u mu\u7889 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c bu\u7897 c c\u7853 u th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n, t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i c\u7853 u n\'f3i trong v\'f4 th\u7913 c h\'f4m qua \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 th\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd ngh\uc0\u297  n\'e0y l\u7841 i l\'e0m c\u7853 u s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u7843  kinh, t\u7921 a nh\u432  th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 v\u7851 n lu\'f4n bao k\'edn n\u7897 i t\'e2m \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7883  l\u7897 t tr\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ngh\uc0\u297  s\'e2u h\u417 n, sau khi \u273 i ra t\u7915  ch\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer l\u7853 p t\u7913 c g\u7885 i cho th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927 . L\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i gi\u7889 ng h\u7879 t Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, c\u361 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch b\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i th\'e1nh l\u7921 c v\'e0 m\'e1u d\u7851 n tranh \u273 \u7845 u trong c\u417  th\u7875 , \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e1u d\u7851 n l\'e0 do Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i n\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f3 c\u7847 u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7913 u. Nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 v\'ec sao, sau khi nghe c\'e2u tr\u7843  l\u7901 i gi\u7889 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nguy\'ean b\uc0\u7843 n hai tu\u7847 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881  gi\u7901  c\'f2n l\u7841 i b\u7889 n ng\'e0y, sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  l\u7841 i k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n li\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm c\u7853 u ch\u417 i, h\u7887 i c\u7853 u \u273 i du l\u7883 ch l\u7847 n n\'e0y th\u7871  n\'e0o, l\u7841 i r\u7911  c\u7853 u c\'f9ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t v\u7883 nh \u7903  m\u7897 t thi\u803  tr\u7845 n nh\u7887  ph\u7909  c\u7853 n l\u432 \u7899 t s\'f3ng hai ng\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i th\uc0\u7853 t, l\u7847 n du l\u7883 ch n\'e0y ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng b\u7883  b\u7855 t \u273 i tham gia m\u7897 t bu\u7893 i t\u7871  t\u7921  k\u7923  qu\'e1i c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, su\'fdt ch\'fat n\u7919 a tr\u7903  th\'e0nh t\u7871  ph\u7849 m, c\'f9ng v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c kh\'f4ng c\u7849 n th\u7853 n u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c th\'e1nh thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a b\u7883  th\u432 \u417 ng, nh\u7919 ng m\u7863 t kh\'e1c r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng t\u7879 . Nh\u432 ng hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\u7847 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n \u273 i ch\u417 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7875  th\u432  gi\'e3n m\u7897 t ch\'fat. Hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\u432 \u7899 t s\'f3ng, h\u7885 c k\u7929  n\u259 ng m\u7899 i s\u7869  l\'e0 bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p t\u7889 t c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m \u273 \u7847 u \'f3c tr\u7903  n\'ean t\u7853 p trung, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian ngh\u297  ng\u7907 i lung tung.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u vui v\u7867  \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, trong th\u7901 i gian hai ng\'e0y n\'e0y qu\u7843  th\u7921 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7845 t \'edt ph\'e2n t\'e2m suy ngh\u297  chuy\u7879 n gi\u7919 a c\u7853 u v\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, ti\u7871 c nu\u7889 i duy nh\u7845 t l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac v\u7873  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u432 a n\u7855 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u297  thu\u7853 t l\u432 \u7899 t s\'f3ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e1n c\uc0\u7847 u Nam \u273 \'e3 d\u7847 n v\'e0o \u273 \'f4ng, th\u7901 i gian tr\u7901 i t\u7889 i ng\'e0y c\'e0ng s\u7899 m, n\u259 m gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i xe bu\'fdt t\u7915  v\u7883 nh trong thi\u803  tr\u7845 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  Sophus, \u432 \u7899 c ch\u7915 ng h\u417 n t\'e1m gi\u7901  l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  v\u7873  \u273 \u7871 n n\u7897 i th\'e0nh Sophus. D\u7885 c con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng h\u7847 u nh\u432  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 n\'fai r\u7915 ng ch\u432 a khai ph\'e1, b\u7903 i v\u7853 y n\'ean kh\'f4ng b\u7883  k\u7865 t xe, tuy nhi\'ean \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'fai quanh co u\u7889 n l\u432 \u7907 n l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ch\'f3ng m\u7863 t, l\'fac \u273 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u297 nh gi\'e1o m\u7897 t l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7875  tr\'e1nh b\u7883  say xe, v\u7915 a l\'ean xe c\u7853 u b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ng\u7911 , b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c \u273 \'e3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c xe ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng ti\u7871 ng va \u273 \u7853 p m\u7841 nh, xe \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7855 c l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i c\uc0\u7917 a s\u7893  l\'e0 khu r\u7915 ng r\u7853 m t\u7889 i \u273 en, m\u7863 t tr\'e1i d\u7921 a v\'e0o th\'e2n n\'fai, m\u7863 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0 c\'e2y c\u7889 i v\'e0 th\u7843 m th\u7921 c v\u7853 t um t\'f9m. Trong r\u7915 ng n\u7893 i l\'ean s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9, ngu\u7891 n s\'e1ng duy nh\u7845 t ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 \'e8n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a xe bu\'fdt l\'e0m cho t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u l\u7901  m\u7901 , c\'e0ng th\'eam nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng r\'f5.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay sang Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i: "L\'e0m sao v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u th\'e1o tai nghe, t\u7887  v\u7867  b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  nghe th\u7845 y l\'e1i xe m\u7855 ng m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, m\u7897 t b\u7841 n h\u7885 c ng\u7891 i b\'ean tr\'e1i l\u7889 i \u273 i nh\u7887  \u7903  gi\u7919 a lo l\u7855 ng nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng. C\u7853 u ta t\'ean Tony, l\'e0 h\u7897 i vi\'ean c\'e2u l\u7841 c b\u7897  l\u432 \u7899 t s\'f3ng \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng, th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean tham gia ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng l\u432 \u7899 t s\'f3ng, \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng t\u7899 i tr\u7845 n nh\u7887  n\'e0y r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n. C\u7853 u ta v\'e0 Giang \u272 i\u7873 n hay n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, c\'f3 ch\'fat giao t\'ecnh. L\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u ta th\u7847 n th\u7847 n b\'ed b\'ed m\'e0 quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Xong r\u7891 i, c\'f3 l\u7869  ch\'fang ta \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i "B\u7885 n c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng" trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
