\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ta n\'f3i ch\'fang l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u7889 n trong n\'fai r\u7915 ng v\'e0 v\'f9ng hoang d\'e3, lang thang th\'e0nh \u273 \'e0n."\cb1 \
