\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra, h\'f4m nay ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7911 a c\u7853 u khi g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y ch\'ednh l\'e0 li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'97\'97 ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 coi \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng tr\u7903  th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  tin t\u432 \u7903 ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u7927  l\u7841 i, m\u7863 c d\'f9 trong b\u7909 ng th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng v\u7851 n th\u7847 m m\u7855 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 "Th\u7907  s\u259 n nh\'e1t gan tr\'ecnh \u273 \u7897  c\'f3 h\u7841 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng tin".\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i h\u7889 i h\u7853 n th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m m\u7899 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y v\'ec mu\u7889 n ti\u234 \u769 t ki\'ea\u803 m m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 ch\u7885 n nh\'e0 m\u7841 ng nghe \u273 \u7891 n t\'edn hi\u7879 u k\'e9m nh\u7845 t nh\u432 ng gi\'e1 c\u7843  ph\u7843 i ch\u259 ng nh\u7845 t, l\'fac \u7845 y c\u7853 u cho r\u7857 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u7881  \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c v\'e0 loanh quanh k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i \u273 \'e2u xa, n\'e0o ng\u7901  b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 i xui x\u7867 o \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7845 p th\u7845 p \u273 \u7841 p v\u7905  l\'fac \u7903  Sydney, nh\u432 ng l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i ch\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, Grey l\u7841 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u432 a cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 i\'ea\u803 n thoa\u803 i m\u417 \u769 i, ngay c\u7843  sim c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m l\u7841 i, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\u7847 n t\u7843 i l\u7841 i nh\u7919 ng \u7913 ng d\u7909 ng c\u7847 n thi\u7871 t, \u273 \u259 ng nh\u7853 p t\'e0i kho\u7843 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u432 a di \u273 \u7897 ng cho c\u7853 u Grey bi\u7875 u l\u7897  v\'f4 c\'f9ng b\'ecnh th\u7843 n, ch\u7881  n\'f3i "Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u7873 n b\'f9 t\u7893 n th\u7845 t cho c\u7853 u" . Nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y gi\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c s\u7869  chu \u273 \'e1o t\u7889 t b\u7909 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\'e0 ai ph\'e2n ph\'f3 v\u7883  qu\u7843 n gia ti\'ean sinh "C\u7893  l\'e3o" n\'e0y \u273 i l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n n\'f3i c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'e2m t\'ecnh c\uc0\u7853 u h\u417 i ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p, r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\u7899  b\u7843 n th\'e2n b\u7883  \'e9p bu\u7897 c b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 \u273 \u7841 t th\'e0nh \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh h\'fat m\'e1u ba m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y v\u7899 i v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  kia, nh\u432 ng v\u7873  sau th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer so v\u7899 i c\u7853 u d\u7921  \u273 o\'e1n c\'f2n t\u7889 t h\u417 n, t\u7889 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac h\'fat m\'e1u \uc0\u273 a s\u7889  th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng, ch\u7881  th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng s\u7869  c\'f3 v\u7867  g\u7845 p g\'e1p. M\u7895 i l\u7847 n h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u thay \u273 \u7893 i m\'f3n \u259 n \u273 a d\u7841 ng, l\u7841 i ki\'ean nh\u7851 n \u273 \'fat cho c\u7853 u \u259 n. H\u7855 n \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i xuy\'ean r\u259 ng nanh qua c\u7893  c\u7853 u, sau \u273 \'f3 d\u7883 u d\'e0ng m\'e0 li\u7871 m mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng, g\u7885 i c\u7853 u b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, h\u7887 i c\u7853 u c\'f3 \u273 au kh\'f4ng, c\'f3 tho\u7843 i m\'e1i kh\'f4ng...\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng l\'fac th\u7871  n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7869  v\u7897 i v\'e0ng l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer n\u7919 a, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i trong l\'f2ng t\u7921  h\u7887 i c\'f3 ph\u7843 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n b\u7883  m\u7855 c ch\u7913 ng Stockholm r\u7891 i hay kh\'f4ng, b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u m\'e0 c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  sinh ra h\u7843 o c\u7843 m \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7897 t con qu\u7927 ; l\u7841 i nghi\'eam t\'fac khuy\'ean nh\u7911  b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng n\'ean b\u7883  h\'ecnh t\u432 \u7907 ng do m\'ecnh t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng ra m\'ea ho\u7863 c, c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'f3 ch\u7881  l\'e0 th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n \'f4n nhu th\u432 \u7901 ng d\'f9ng c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u gi\'e0 \u273 \u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \'e3i v\u7899 i con m\u7891 i, \u273 \u7915 ng qu\'ean Alex tr\u432 \u7899 c khi b\u7883  v\u7841 ch tr\u7847 n c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng l\'e0 h\'e0ng x\'f3m nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh, b\u7841 n h\u7885 c th\'e2n thi\u7879 n...\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\'f9ng l\'fac \u273 \'f3 trong l\'f2ng c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t \'e2m thanh y\u7871 u \u7899 t ph\u7843 n b\'e1c, \u273 \'e1m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bao gi\u7901  tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p h\'fat m\'e1u t\u7915  c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u n\'f3i h\u7855 n l\u7841 nh nh\u7841 t v\'f4 t\'ecnh, ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841  kh\'f3 g\u7847 n; th\u7871  nh\u432 ng m\u7895 i l\u7847 n h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7911 a m\'e0y, c\'f2n cho m\'e0y \u259 n, mang y ph\u7909 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n cho m\'e0y m\u7863 c...\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 m\uc0\u7895 i l\'fac b\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer h\'fat m\'e1u, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'fac nghe th\u7845 y gi\u7885 ng h\u7855 n, b\u7843 n th\'e2n s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7863 t n\'f3ng l\'ean, ph\'e1t nhi\u7879 t, tim \u273 \u7853 p nhanh h\u417 n, l\'fac r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i c\u259 n ph\'f2ng kia, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng kh\'f4ng th\'f4i sau khi \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7855 n \u273 \'fat m\'e1u c\'e0ng l\'ean t\u7899 i \u273 \u7881 nh \u273 i\u7875 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\'e1n gh\'e9t b\u7843 n th\'e2n, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7843 n th\'e2n qu\u7843  th\u7921 c gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ti\u7875 u nam sinh nh\'e1t gan m\u7899 i l\'ean trung h\u7885 c t\u432 \u417 ng t\u432  hoa kh\'f4i c\u7911 a tr\u432 \u7901 ng\'97\'97 "Hoa kh\'f4i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u259 n c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng h\u7885 c nh\'f3m c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd \u259 n chung v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, h\u7885 c c\'f9ng m\'ecnh, c\'f2n c\'f9ng m\'ecnh v\u7873  nh\'e0... C\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\'f4 \u7845 y c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'ecnh r\u7845 t \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t kh\'f4ng?" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i thi\u7871 u n\u7919  xinh \u273 \u7865 p \u273 \u417 n thu\u7847 n g\'ec \u273 \'f3. C\u7853 u v\u7851 n n\'ean mau ch\'f3ng d\u7915 ng nh\u7919 ng \'fd ni\u7879 m kh\'f4ng t\u432 \u7903 ng trong \u273 \u7847 u n\'e0y l\u7841 i \u273 i. C\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  m\u7855 c ch\u7913 ng Stockholm, \u273 \u7907 i ho\'e0n th\'e0nh \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh qu\u7927  d\u7883  kia, b\u7883  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c ti\'eau tr\u7915  tr\'ed nh\u7899 , r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i v\u7883  th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  n\u7885 ... T\u7921  nhi\'ean m\u7885 i th\u7913  s\u7869  \u7893 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\'e2m s\u7921  v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n th\u7907  s\u259 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u ph\u7843 i n\'f3i th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \'e2y, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  n\'f3i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, em mu\u7889 n th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n v\u7899 i anh m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n. Kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian tr\u432 \u7899 c em v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng gi\u7845 c m\u417  kh\'f4ng hay v\u7899 i anh, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  em l\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\u7845 t c\'f3 h\u7843 o c\u7843 m v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, h\'ecnh nh\u432  em... th\'edch h\u7855 n m\u7845 t r\u7891 i.. Anh n\'f3i xem em \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 b\u7883  l\'e0m sao? C\'f3 ph\u7843 i sau khi b\u7883  x\'f3a tr\'ed nh\u7899 , r\u7901 i \u273 i r\u7891 i s\u7869  kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng?" Ch\u7881  e r\u7857 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i nghe th\u7845 y n\u7917 a c\'e2u \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e3 qu kinh h\'e3i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao. N\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f2n tuy\u7879 t giao lu\'f4n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u v\'ec sao sau khi \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i t\u432  b\u7843 n ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 i nhanh ch\'f3ng sa \u273 \u7885 a th\'e0nh d\u7841 ng n\'e0y, kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  m\u417  m\u7897 ng linh tinh \u273 \u7871 n b\u7841 n m\'ecnh trong m\u417 , ngo\'e0i hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c c\'f2n sinh ra l\u432 u luy\u7871 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i ra kh\'f4ng d\'e1m th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  \'97\'97 qu\u7843  th\u7921 c c\u7863 n b\'e3, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t lo\u7841 i n\'e0y c\'f3 t\'ednh l\'e0 ch\'e2n \u273 \u7913 ng hai thuy\u7873 n kh\'f4ng n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec \uc0\u273 \u7875  gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t phi\u7873 n mu\u7897 n l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta th\u7921 c s\u7921  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh tham gia chuy\u7871 n \u273 i ch\u417 i l\u432 \u7899 t s\'f3ng, ai ng\u7901  l\u7841 i \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ki\uc0\u7871 p tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7855 c c\u7853 u h\u7859 n l\'e0 c\'f3 c\u7915 u o\'e1n v\u7899 i qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh v\u7851 n \u273 ang truy v\u7845 n v\u7873  b\u7885 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u432 \u7899 p ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tony d\uc0\u7913 t kho\'e1t ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng gh\u7871  tr\u7889 ng ph\'eda sau b\u7885 n h\u7885 , di\u7877 n gi\u7843 i k\u7929  c\'e0ng: "Nghe \u273 \u7891 n trong n\'fai c\'f3 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, b\u7885 n ch\'fang xu\u7845 t qu\u7927  nh\u7853 p th\u7847 n, xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n v\'e0o bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i tr\'ean nh\u7919 ng con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\u7855 ng \'edt xe c\u7897 , ch\u7863 n xe l\u7841 i, h\'fat m\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i trong xe, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i x\'f3a tr\'ed nh\u7899  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  th\u7843  \u273 i. Nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i may m\u7855 n tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ki\u7871 p m\'e0 kh\'f4ng b\u7883  x\'f3a tr\'ed nh\u7899 , cho n\'ean nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n \u273 \u7841 i v\u7873  "B\u7885 n c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng" n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c truy\u7873 n ra. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i lu\'f4n th\u7853 t gi\u7843  kh\'f3 l\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ai th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng ng\uc0\u7901  l\u7841 i l\'e0 th\u7853 t." C\u7853 u l\u7849 m b\u7849 m, "B\u7885 n c\u432 \u7899 p m\'e1u, c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e1i xe l\'e0 m\uc0\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng trung ni\'ean da tr\u7855 ng d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i to l\u7899 n, \'f4ng c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng d\u7915 ng xe, c\u7843 nh b\'e1o t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7903  c\u7917 a s\u7893 , kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c xu\u7889 ng xe, nghe t\u7915  ti\u7871 ng vang v\u7915 a r\u7891 i ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n xe \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o v\u7853 t g\'ec \u273 \'f3, \'f4ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m xu\u7889 ng xe th\u259 m d\'f2. Ch\u7841 y \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'fai trong \u273 \'eam \u273 \u7871 n l\'e3o luy\u7879 n, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean \'f4ng c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 .\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 trong r\u7915 ng c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng lan r\u7897 ng, m\'e0n s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng g\u7847 n nh\u432  bao ph\u7911  k\'edn xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e1i xe nh\'ecn m\'e0n s\uc0\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, t\u7855 t m\'e1y, c\u361 ng t\u7855 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \'e8n trong ngo\'e0i, hi v\u7885 ng l\'e0m v\u7853 y s\u7869  gi\'fap \u7849 n xe \u273 i. C\'f3 h\'e0nh kh\'e1ch \u273 \u7883 nh g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7847 u c\u7913 u, l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'edn hi\u7879 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e1i xe t\uc0\u7915  tr\'ean gh\u7871  l\'e1i \u273 i xu\u7889 ng, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng d\u7863 n d\'f2 m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng n\'ean ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0 \'e1nh s\'e1ng. L\u7853 p t\u7913 c \'e1nh s\'e1ng tr\u7855 ng t\u7915  c\'e1c thi\u7871 t b\u7883  \u273 i\u7879 n t\u7917  \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, c\u7843  xe ch\'ecm v\'e0o trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i, ti\u7871 ng h\'edt th\u7903  c\u7911 a m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng nghe th\uc0\u7845 y trong s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng x\u7897 t xo\u7841 t, c\u7853 u nh\'edu m\'e0y quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en \u273 ang b\'e1m l\'ean c\u7917 a s\u7893  xe b\'ean ph\u7843 i m\'ecnh, tr\'ean c\u7917 a s\u7893  th\u7911 y tinh in r\'f5 m\u7897 t g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng xanh, r\u259 ng nanh r\u7845 t d\'e0i \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong con m\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \u7887  s\u7853 m c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\'f3e l\'ean s\u7921  tham lam, h\u7855 n nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\u7843 o \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7845 t ng\u7901  kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u. C\u7853 u c\u7889  n\'e9n kh\'f4ng di chuy\u7875 n \'e1nh m\u7855 t, ch\u7881  l\u7863 ng l\u7869  gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t y\u7871 t h\u7847 u, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng duy tr\'ec tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh t\u7915  t\u7915  \u273 \u432 a tay tr\'e1i l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean ng\'f3n \'e1p \'fat tay tr\'e1i c\'f3 chi\uc0\u7871 c nh\u7851 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 eo cho c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 t\'edn v\u7853 t, c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  c\'f3 c\'f4ng d\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i nhanh nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \'e3 ph\u7843 i s\u7917  d\u7909 ng, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng hay kh\'f4ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7853 n l\u7921 c kh\u7855 c ch\u7871  c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng, lo l\u7855 ng b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, c\u7853 u y\'ean l\u7863 ng c\u7889  \'fd quay m\u7863 t nh\u7851 n in b\u7909 i gai hoa h\u7891 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda con qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f4i \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7917  \u273 \u7887  s\u7853 m c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c m\u7903  l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p d\'e1n m\u7863 t nh\u7851 n l\'ean c\u7917 a s\u7893 , \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\'ecn c\'e0ng th\'eam r\'f5.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh th\u7853 t s\u7921  m\u7841 o hi\u7875 m. \u272 \'e2y d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 t\'edn v\u7853 t c\u7911 a th\u7907  s\u259 n, m\'e0 c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng r\'f5 lai l\u7883 ch b\u7885 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng k\u7871 t th\'f9 v\u7899 i gia t\u7897 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i s\u7869  d\u7851 n t\u7899 i b\u7883  c\u7855 n tr\u7843 , Tony n\'f3i nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  n\'e0y ch\u7881  l\u7845 y m\'e1u, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\'f9y ti\u7879 n h\u7841 i m\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 o\'e1n b\u7885 n ch\'fang c\u361 ng s\u7907  g\'e2y ra phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c qu\'e1 l\u7899 n n\'ean m\u7899 i h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Nh\u432 ng vi\u7879 c m\'ecnh \u273 \u432 a nh\u7851 n ra r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n to\'e0n b\u7897  ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean xe g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i ki\u7871 p n\u7841 n l\u7899 n h\u417 n, m\'e0 ch\'ednh m\'ecnh l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c b\u7843 o v\u7879  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat h\uc0\u7889 i h\u7853 n h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng li\u7873 u l\u297 nh b\u7889 c \u273 \u7891 ng c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n, nh\u432 ng th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u \u273 ang \'e2m th\u7847 m h\u7889 i h\u7853 n, con qu\u7927  kia ch\u7907 t lui kh\u7887 i m\u7863 t k\'ednh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong m\'e0n s\uc0\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c l\u7841 i vang l\'ean ti\u7871 ng x\u7897 t xo\u7841 t v\'e0 ti\u7871 ng c\'e0nh c\'e2y lo\u7841 t xo\u7841 t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 th\u7875  lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng nghe th\u7845 y v\'e0i t\u7915  ti\u7871 ng Anh.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 To\'e0n b\uc0\u7897  ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean xe ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c s\u7907  h\'e3i ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n c\u7911 a t\'e0i x\u7871 , d\'f9ng \'e1nh m\u7855 t v\'e0 \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c th\u7875  hi\u7879 n n\u7895 i s\u7907  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\u7899 i b\u7841 n h\u7885 c. Trong b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u361 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y qu\'e1i v\u7853 t d\'e1n tr\'ean c\u7917 a s\u7893  kia\'97\'97 kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  m\u7897 t con, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec. C\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y qua h\u417 n m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat, s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 d\u7847 n tan, l\u7897  ra \'e1nh tr\u259 ng s\'e1ng trong v\u7855 t tr\'ean cao.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'e0i x\uc0\u7871  l\u7845 y l\u7841 i b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n l\u7845 y \u273 \'e8n pin d\u7921  ph\'f2ng, m\u7903  c\u7917 a tr\u432 \u7899 c xem x\'e9t m\u7897 t h\u7891 i\'97\'97 t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec, t\u7921 a nh\u432  m\'e0n s\u432 \u417 ng d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng b\'f3ng \u273 en x\u7897 t xo\u7841 t tr\'e0n t\u7899 i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng quay v\uc0\u7873  xe, ch\'e0 x\'e1t hai tay, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng l\u7847 m b\u7847 m m\u7845 y c\'e2u, kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng l\u7841 i xe, m\u7903  t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \'e8n trong ngo\'e0i, l\'e1i xe ch\u7841 y tr\'ean con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng quen thu\u7897 c nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi. Qua n\u7917 a gi\u7901  sau \'f4ng l\u7841 i m\u7903  nh\u7841 c. \'cdt nh\u7845 t cho \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u \u7893 n, c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u n\u7919 a l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  b\'ecnh an v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Theo ti\uc0\u7871 ng nh\u7841 c \u273 \u7891 ng qu\'ea vang l\'ean, trong xe kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c l\u7841 i sinh kh\'ed v\'e0 s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u361 ng c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, c\'e1c h\'e0nh kh\'e1ch r\u7889 i r\'edt l\'ean m\u7841 ng ho\u7863 c g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho b\u7841 n b\'e8 k\u7875  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n qu\u7927  d\u7883  b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\u7915 a g\u7863 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 n tin cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7843 m \u417 n chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, c\u361 ng m\u432 \u7907 n c\u417  h\u7897 i gi\u7843  b\u7897  nh\u432  nh\'e2n ti\u7879 n m\'e0 h\u7887 i m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  ch\'ednh m\'ecnh v\u7851 n mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i: " \u431 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7911 a em v\'e0 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer sau khi ho\'e0n th\'e0nh, s\u7869  b\u7883  x\'f3a tr\'ed nh\u7899  \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7853 u ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y trong l\'f2ng, nh\u432 ng t\u7915  sau l\u7847 n B\u7841 ch Thu h\u7887 i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  n\'e0y, c\u7853 u l\u7841 i lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 nh\u7899  k\u7929 . C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  l\u7841 c quan nh\u432  bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t B\u7841 ch Thu.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Chuy\uc0\u7879 n n\'e0y quy\u7873 n quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh thu\u7897 c v\u7873  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, n\u7871 u h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u qu\'ean, v\u7853 y c\u7853 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'ean."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em hi\uc0\u7875 u r\u7891 i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7855 n tin, "C\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c, Ngh\'eanh Chi, chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u lang thang l\u7847 n n\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean anh \u273 \u7915 ng b\'e1o c\'e1o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng, gi\'fap em \u273 \u7875  \'fd x\u7917  l\'fd vi\u7879 c sau \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'ec sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em mu\uc0\u7889 n c\u7847 u Emmer ra tay."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\'f9y h\u7913 ng, l\'e0 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m \u273 ang n\u7855 m quy\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c kia khi g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7843 o c\u7853 u \u273 i c\u7847 u Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer gi\'fap c\u7853 u lu\'f4n lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n, nh\u432 ng l\u7847 n n\'e0y l\u7841 i nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c maf ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 i t\'ecm \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao nh\uc0\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh t\'f4i s\u7869  r\u7901 i \u273 i, d\'f9 sao nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh t\'f4i s\u7869  qu\'ean h\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao t\'f4i c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7881  tr\u259 m n\u259 m tu\u7893 i th\u7885 , \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\'e0i ch\u7881  l\'e0 ch\u7889 c l\'e1t m\'e0 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean \'edt nh\uc0\u7845 t t\'f4i mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 t gi\u7901  kh\u7855 c n\'e0y, t\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m t\'f4i c\'f2n nh\u7899  r\'f5, t\'f4i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\'e0i, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t hay kh\'f4ng, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat quy\u7873 n h\u7841 n t\'f9y h\u7913 ng hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Emmer, t\'f4i nh\uc0\u7853 n thua.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t k\u7875  l\'e0 ch\u7913 ng Stockholm hay l\'e0 g\'ec, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  t\'f4i, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c c\'f3 ch\'fat...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m m\u7855 t, \u273 \'fang l\'fac ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i nh\u7919 ng suy t\u432 \u7903 ng trong l\'f2ng. C\u7853 u c\u7845 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, d\u7921 a v\'e0o gh\u7871  nh\u7887  h\u7865 p nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u qua b\'ean ph\u7843 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe \uc0\u273 \'e3 v\'e0o n\u7897 i th\'e0nh Sophus, c\u7917 a s\u7893  xe ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0u cam \u7843 m \u273 \u7841 m, c\u361 ng ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t m\u7901  m\u7883 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chung quy c\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m minh x\'e1c th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n m\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n l\'f2ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ch\uc0\u7919  kia, d\'f9 l\'e0 t\u7921  m\'ecnh ngh\u297  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m.\cb1 \
