\f9\b \cf4 Ch\uc0\u432 \u417 ng 87: Ba ng\'e0y \u273 \u7871 m ng\u432 \u7907 c\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 L\'fac xe bu\'fdt \uc0\u273 \u7871 n b\u7871 n trung t\'e2m Sophus \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  t\u7889 i, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\u7889  r\u7845 t v\u7855 ng v\u7867 , c\u417  b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng hay xe c\u7897 . Nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  h\u417 i th\u7845 p, m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n gi\'f3 th\u7893 i qua, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\'e9o k\'e9o qu\u7847 n \'e1o. Nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 gi\u7843 m, tr\u432 \u7899 c h\'f4m c\u7853 u r\u7901 i Sophus h\'ecnh nh\u432  kh\'f4ng l\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f9ng Giang \u272 i\u7873 n r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i b\u7871 n xe bu\'fdt, l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng ra xem, taxi c\u7853 u h\u7865 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 l\u7869  s\u7855 p \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3i v\u7899 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n: "\u272 \u7841 i Giang, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i t\'f4i k\u7875  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\u7873  v\u7899 i b\u7841 n c\u7911 a cha t\'f4i, b\'e1c \u7845 y r\u7845 t lo l\u7855 ng, b\u7843 o t\'f4i h\'f4m nay qua ch\u7895  b\'e1c \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u7853 u l\u7841 i b\u7893  sung: "Ng\'e0y mai b\'e1c \u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881 , \u273 \'fang l\'fac mu\u7889 n mang t\'f4i ra ngo\'e0i ch\u417 i. H\u417 n n\u7919 a ng\'e0y khai gi\u7843 ng t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u7899 p n\'ean c\'f3 l\u7869  ba ng\'e0y t\u7899 i \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng v\u7873 , c\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng lo l\u7855 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i "B\u7841 n c\u7911 a cha" n\'e0y l\'e0 c\u7853 u b\u7883 a ra l\'fac ng\u7911  l\u7841 i ch\u7895  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i gi\u7901  l\u7841 i ph\u7843 i d\'f9ng \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n qu\u7843  nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ho\'e0i nghi: "V\u7853 y c\u7853 u c\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i th\'ec nh\u7855 n tin cho t\'f4i. Ng\'e0y mai \u273 i ch\u417 i vui v\u7867  nh\'e9." N\'f3i xong c\u361 ng ph\u7845 t ph\u7845 t tay, m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda b\u7871 n xe, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  b\u7841 n m\'ecnh mu\u7889 n \u273 i g\u7863 p m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hi\uc0\u7879 n t\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 nh\u7899  r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7871 n t\'f2a nh\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, gi\u7919 a \u273 \'eam khuya c\u361 ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng l\'e1i xe \u273 \u7871 n c\u7893 ng ch\'ednh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey hi\uc0\u7875 n nhi\'ean r\u7845 t kinh ng\u7841 c vi\u7879 c n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n th\u259 m, k\'e9o c\u7917 a \u273 \u7875  nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 l\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n to\'e0n th\'e2n \u273 \'f4ng c\u7913 ng \u273 i v\'e0o: "Sao c\u7853 u l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y gi\u7901  n\'e0y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7897  \u7845 m trong ph\'f2ng nhanh ch\'f3ng xua tan h\u417 i l\u7841 nh tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, d\'f9 v\u7853 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 ti\u7871 n th\'eam v\'e0i b\u432 \u7899 c v\u7873  ph\'eda l\'f2 s\u432 \u7903 i, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng nh\u7855 n tin b\'e1o cho Giang \u272 i\u7873 n. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t m\u7845 y ng\'e0y t\u7899 i c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  th\u7845 y ch\u7913  \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3i l\'e0 d\'f9ng di \u273 \u7897 ng: "T\'f4i \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, t\'f4i c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n mu\u7889 n n\'f3i v\u7899 i ng\'e0i \u7845 y, \'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7875  th\'f4ng b\'e1o gi\'fap t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey b\uc0\u7843 o c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng sofa, mang cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\u7889 c h\u7891 ng tr\'e0 n\'f3ng: "C\u7853 u ch\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ta \u273 i b\'e1o \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, ng\u7891 i tr\'ean sofa c\u7847 m c\u7889 c s\u7913  tinh x\u7843 o u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m, l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c nh\u7853 n ra vi\u7879 c m\'ecnh \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng k\u7923  qu\'e1i m\'e0 li\u7873 u l\u297 nh c\u7905  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e1t sau Grey t\u7915  l\u7847 u hai \u273 i xu\u7889 ng, \u273 \u432 a tay ra hi\u7879 u m\u7901 i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  huy\u7873 n quan, kh\'f4ng \u273 i ti\u7871 p v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7901  c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  t\u7921  \u273 \u7897 ng kh\'e9p l\u7841 i nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi, c\u7853 u ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i qu\u7901  tay \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, sau \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n \'e1p l\'ean c\u7917 a, l\u7897  ra ph\u7847 n g\'e1y tr\u7855 ng m\u7873 m m\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng ch\'fat kh\'e1ng c\u7921 , t\u432  th\'e1i nh\u432  \u273 ang hi\u7871 n t\u7871 , gi\u7889 ng m\u7897 t con nai nh\u7887  ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng n\u7857 m tr\'ean t\u7871  \u273 \'e0n, l\u7897  ra nh\u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7875 m ch\'ed m\u7841 ng cho ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u432 \u7903 ng ngo\u7841 n. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean n\'f3i g\'ec, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \'97\'97 t\u7915  m\u7897 t kh\u7855 c c\u7853 u v\'e0o c\u7917 a, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean, c\u7853 u nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng nhanh ch\'f3n \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n. Ngay sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7897 t lu\u7891 ng l\u432 \u803 c k\'e9o t\u7899 i, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u d\'f9ng tay tr\'e1i \'f4m th\u7855 t l\u432 ng c\u7853 u, tay ph\u7843 i vu\u7889 t ve ph\u7847 n g\'e1y, c\'e0ng d\'f9ng s\u7913 c m\'e0 \u273 \'e8 c\u7853 u l\'ean c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u259 ng nanh \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7889 ng tay ph\u7843 i l\'ean tr\'e1n, kh\u7855 c ch\u7871  ch\'ednh m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t ra \'e2m thanh, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng r\'ean k\'ecm kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i t\u7915  tr\'e0n ra t\u7915  mi\u7879 ng. C\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u l\u7847 n n\'e0y d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\'f2n c\u432 \u7901 ng li\u7879 t h\u417 n so v\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ngh\u297  c\u7853 u \u273 \'fang l\'e0 \u273 i\'ean r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nguy\'ean nh\'e2n g\'ec, l\u7841 i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh mu\u7889 n ki\u7871 m c\u7899  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, c\'f2n \u273 \u7875  cho con qu\u7927  n\'e0y h\'fat m\'e1u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng m\u7855 c ch\u7913 ng nghi\u7879 n b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u nh\u432  l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n ngh\u297  c\'e1ch \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7921 c k\u7923  kh\'f3 ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n trong l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n n\'e0y. . . D\'f9 b\u7883  h\u7855 n h\'fat m\'e1u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng c\u7921 , kh\'f4ng ch\'e1n gh\'e9t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n l\'e0 t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u mu\u7889 n tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac qu\'ean h\u7871 t, l\u7841 i g\u7847 n Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c n\'e0y th\'eam m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qua m\uc0\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\u7899 i r\'fat r\u259 ng nanh ra, v\u7915 a d\'f9ng ng\'f3n c\'e1i th\u7845 m n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t vu\u7889 t l\'ean mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng v\u7915 a nh\'e0n nh\u7841 t h\u7887 i: "Mu\u7897 n th\u7871  n\'e0y l\u7841 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i, v\u7915 a t\u7899 i \u273 \'e3 ngoan ngo\'e3n \u273 \u7875  ta h\'fat m\'e1u ng\u432 \u417 i tr\u432 \u7899 c. L\u7841 i l\'e0 v\'ec chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng tr\uc0\u7843  l\u7901 i m\'e0 ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i, th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 \u273 \u432 a tay \'f4m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, kh\u7869  ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u tho\'e1ng h\'f4n l\'ean b\'ean m\u7863 t h\u7855 n, nh\u432  con th\'fa nh\u7887  c\u7849 n th\u7853 n mu\u7889 n l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i vui.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong m\uc0\u361 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\u7869  "H\u7915 " m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng b\u7845 t m\'e3n, tr\'e1i l\u7841 i, h\u7855 n r\u7845 t h\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7909  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , " Tr\'ec Di\'ean y\'ean l\'f2ng, v\u7851 n duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  v\'f9i v\'e0o vai \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i, "T\u7889 i nay tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\u7873  t\'f4i g\u7863 p m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u lang thang t\u7853 p k\'edch ng\u432 \u7901 i, ng\'e0i c\'f3 th\u7875  hay gi\'fap t\'f4i tr\u7915 ng tr\u7883  b\u7885 n ch\'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean d\'f9ng l\u7921 c b\u7871  ngang c\u7853 u l\'ean, \u273 i v\'e0i b\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n sofa ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean qua m\u7897 t b\'ean m\'e0 ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, vu\u7889 t ve g\'e1y c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "L\'e0 v\'ec ch\'fat chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e0 v\'ec ch\'fat chuy\uc0\u7879 n n\'e0y? H\u7843 ?" H\u7855 n v\u7915 a l\u7863 p l\u7841 i v\u7915 a nh\u7865  gi\u7885 n th\u7847 m th\'ec, "Ta kh\'f4ng tin, v\u7915 a ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng quay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7875  ta h\'fat m\'e1u v\u7915 a ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng h\'f4n, nghe l\u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y ch\u7881  v\'ec ch\'fat chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, ta kh\'f4ng tin."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean n\'f3i ti\u7871 p nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o. C\u7853 u h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng, \u273 ang mu\u7889 n tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, l\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u7847 m tay tr\'e1i m\'ecnh l\'ean, kh\u7869  vu\u7889 t ve chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n tr\'ean ng\'f3n \'e1p \'fat: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f2n c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n l\'e0 th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  sao? Ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f2n \u273 eo nh\u7851 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n. Lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \'e2u c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i t\u7899 i t\'ecm ta."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Emmer c\u361 ng tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c m\u7897 t gi\'e2y, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\u7841 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "Ta m\u7899 i ngh\u297  ra. . . t\u7863 ng ng\u432 \u417 i nh\u7851 n, h\u7855 n l\'e0 c\u7847 u h\'f4n ng\u432 \u417 i sao? Ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n l\u7901 i r\u7891 i sao? C\'f2n ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i \'f4m ta h\'f4n ta, ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i, b\u7841 n trai ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f3 bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng? Li\u7879 u c\'f3 kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u kh\'f4ng? \'c0, ng\u432 \u417 i c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n d\'f9 c\'f3 bi\u7871 t r\'f5 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? D\'f9 sao h\u7855 n \u273 \'e1nh kh\'f4ng l\u7841 i ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7845 t \'edt khi nghe Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer n\'f3i l\u7901 i d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n l\'e0 l\u7901 i tho\'e1ng ch\u7871  nh\u7841 o nh\u432  l\'fac n\'e0y, n\u7909  h\'f4n v\'e0 c\'e1i \'f4m v\u7915 a r\u7891 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n x\'fac \u273 \u7897 ng ng\'e2y ng\u7889 c l\'e0m ra \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh l\'fd do tr\'e0o ph\'fang cho h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7893  h\u7885 ng tho\'e1ng ngh\u7865 n, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'e3i l\u7841 i: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i, anh \u7845 y ch\u7881  coi t\'f4i l\'e0 b\u7841 n, t\'f4i c\u361 ng ch\u7881  coi anh \u7845 y l\'e0 b\u7841 n, c\u7843  hai l\'e0 quan h\u7879  b\u7841 n b\'e8 thu\u7847 n t\'fay. Anh \u7845 y \u273 \u432 a nh\u7851 n cho t\'f4i ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\'ec mu\u7889 n b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'f4i, n\u7871 u nh\u432  l\u7847 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n \u273 \'f3, c\'f3 l\u7869  ng\'e0i c\u361 ng s\u7869  ch\u7859 ng th\u7875  h\'fat m\'e1u t\'f4i n\u7919 a.."\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y ta \u273 \'e2y th\u7853 t ph\u7843 i c\'e1m \u417 n h\u7855 n." \'c2m thanh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\u7841 nh nh\u7841 t m\'e0 \u432 u nh\'e3, l\u7897  ra s\u7921  th\u7901  \u417  th\u7845 u x\u432 \u417 ng, "Ch\u7881  l\'e0 b\u7841 n? B\u7841 n \u273 eo nh\u7851 n cho ng\u432 \u417 i? C\u361 ng l\'e0 b\u7841 n m\'e0 ng\u432 \u417 i n\u7857 m m\u417  g\u7885 i t\'ean h\u7855 n, g\u7885 i h\u7855 n l\'e3o c\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n th\'e2n m\u7853 t m\'e0 \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, trong mi\u7879 ng l\u7841 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n kia, t\u7921 a nh\u432  \u273 ang mu\u7889 n \'e9p h\u7887 i t\u7915  trong mi\u7879 ng c\u7853 u vi\u7879 c g\'ec \u273 \'f3: "Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i, ng\u432 \u417 i cho r\u7857 ng t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'f3i l\'fac m\u417  ng\u7911  ta kh\'f4ng h\u7873  nghe th\u7845 y sao? Ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ng\u432 \u417 i qua \u273 \'eam \u7903  \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 ai \'f4m ng\u432 \u417 i ph\u7911  ch\u259 n cho ng\u432 \u417 i? V\u7853 y ra hai ng\u432 \u417 i l\'e0 l\u432 \u7905 ng t\'ecnh t\u432 \u417 ng duy\u7879 t ? K\u7871 t qu\u7843  ng\u432 \u417 i b\u7883  \u7911 y khu\u7845 t, l\u7841 i ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm ta b\'e0y ra b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y, v\'ec sao? H\u7843 ? Nghe l\u7901 i, n\'f3i cho ta bi\u7871 t, l\'e0 v\'ec sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi\'eang m\uc0\u7863 t, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong ng\u7921 c m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n l\u7841 nh m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n n\'f3ng. C\u7853 u ngh\u297  m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 gi\u7843 i th\'edch kh\'f4ng r\'f5, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o gi\u7843 i th\'edch nh\u7919 ng gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng kia c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, ngo\'e0i hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c c\u7853 u \u273 \'edch \u273 \'edch x\'e1c x\'e1c r\u7845 t c\u7849 n th\u7853 n quy c\u7911  m\'e0 l\'e0m b\u7841 n v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u432 ng trong m\u7897 ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 d\'e1ng v\u7867  gi\u7889 ng h\u7879 t th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  l\u7841 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau th\'e2n m\u7853 t v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, m\'e0 c\u7853 u c\u361 ng thu\u7853 n theo \u273 \'f3n nh\u7853 n t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh trong m\u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 c\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n chu \u273 \'e1o \u273 \'e1ng tin c\u7853 y, nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n c\u7913 u c\u7853 u trong l\'fac nguy nan, c\u7853 u \u7903  trong m\u7897 ng \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \'e3i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ta nh\u432  th\u7871  v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7893  th\u7865 n, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang. M\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 c\u7853 u ph\u7841 m ph\u7843 i, n\'f3i m\u7899  c\u361 ng \u273 \'edch x\'e1c l\'e0 c\u7853 u n\'f3i, b\u7843 o c\u7853 u \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u361 ng l\'e0 n\'f3i d\u7889 i, ch\'ednh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng tin. Cho n\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  bi\u7879 n gi\u7843 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch quan tr\u7885 ng nh\u7845 t m\'ecnh t\u7899 i n\u417 i n\'e0y, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n quan tr\u7885 ng n\u7919 a, Emmer cho r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u th\'edch Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao, d\'f9 sao th\u7901 i gian c\'f2n l\u7841 i cho c\u7853 u v\'e0 con qu\u7927  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m. Tranh lu\u7853 n, gi\u7843 i th\'edch v\u7899 i h\u7855 n c\'f2n kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng qu\'fd tr\u7885 ng th\u7901 i gian c\'f2n l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u tu\u7897 t xu\u7889 ng t\u7915  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, ng\u7891 i v\'e0o b\'ean c\u7841 nh, t\u7915  sau l\u432 ng \'f4m l\u7845 y h\u7855 n, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i \'e1p l\'ean, \u273 \u7847 u c\u361 ng d\'e1n tr\'ean l\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: ". . . \u272 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , t\'f4i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 mu\u7889 n n\'f3i, ch\u7881  c\'f2n ba ng\'e0y n\u7919 a \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7911 a ch\'fang ta s\u7869  k\u7871 t th\'fac. Ng\'e0i \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i, sau khi \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t s\u7869  \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i r\u7901 i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean t\u7881 nh ng\u7897  \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n ng\'e0y cu\u7889 i, ch\u7881  s\u7907  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n \u273 ang l\u7915 a g\u7841 t ch\'ednh m\'ecnh, l\u7915 a g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, ch\u7881  s\u7907  c\u7853 u v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n r\u7857 ng, c\u7853 u luy\u7871 n ti\u7871 c qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, con qu\u7927  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n n\u7893 i danh t\'e0n nh\u7851 n x\u7843 o tr\'e1, \u273 \u7871 n nay ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng l\u7897  m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u417  th\u7875  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u tho\'e1ng c\u7913 ng l\u7841 i, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i: "Ra v\u7853 y. Qu\u7843  nhi\'ean ng\u432 \u417 i v\u7851 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y. Y\'ean t\'e2m, ta s\u7869  tu\'e2n th\u7911  \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh, an an to\'e0n to\'e0n, ho\'e0n ho\'e0n ch\u7881 nh ch\u7881 nh m\'e0 th\u7843  ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7849 y ng\'e3 nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i ng\u7917 a m\u7863 t tr\'ean sofa, m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a \'e1p l\'ean m\u7863 c s\u7913 c m\'e0 h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7855 n r\u7845 t d\'f9ng s\u7913 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t m\u7921 c c\u7889  g\u7855 ng k\'ecm n\'e9n kh\'f4ng r\'ean ra ti\u7871 n nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi. Tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 ch\u7881  c\u7847 n c\u7853 u t\u7887  v\u7867  kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c th\u7843  l\u7887 ng l\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sofa nh\uc0\u7887  h\u7865 p, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u sau khi r\'fat r\u259 ng nanh ra li\u7873 n n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng song song c\u7841 nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, h\u7855 n g\u7847 n nh\u432  \u273 em ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a b\u7883  h\'fat m\'e1u \'f4m v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c. V\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u7871 n khi h\'fat m\'e1u ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t, l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i h\u7887 i \u273 i\u7873 u \u273 \'e3 c\u7845 t gi\u7919  r\u7845 t l\'e2u: "Emmer, \u273 \u7907 i \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh ho\'e0n th\'e0nh, t\'f4i s\u7869  b\u7883  x\'f3a h\u7871 t tr\'ed nh\u7899  li\'ean quan sao? V\u7873  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, v\u7873 . . . ng\'e0i?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u h\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7863 t v\'e0o l\u432 ng gh\u7871 , Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \'f4m c\u7853 u t\u7915  ph\'eda sau, \'e2m thanh nhu h\'f2a, Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c v\u7915 a m\u7899 i u\u7889 ng no m\'e1u l\'fac n\'e0o c\u361 ng r\u7845 t d\u7877  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n: "Ng\u432 \u417 i th\'ec sao? Ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f3 mu\u7889 n qu\'ean kh\'f4ng? B\u7843 o b\u7889 i, ta c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng ng\u432 \u417 i, vi\u7879 c n\'e0y do ng\u432 \u417 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c r\u7845 t l\'e2u, m\u7897 t l\'fac sau m\u7899 i nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "Qu\'ean. Emmer, \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i qu\'ean \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c d\'f9ng r\u259 ng vu\u7889 t ve ph\u7847 n g\'e1y c\u7853 u, h\u417 i n\'e2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "Ta bi\u7871 t m\'e0, ng\u432 \u417 i c\u259 m gh\'e9t ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i, trong \'e2m thanh l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nghe ra h\u7881  n\u7897 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3 cao h\u7913 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e2y ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean v\'f4 ngh\u297 a. Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\'f2ng m\'ecnh nh\'f3i \u273 au t\u7915 ng tr\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i c\u259 m gh\'e9t. . . M\'e0 l\'e0. . . Th\'edch ng\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'edch m\uc0\u7897 t con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng n\'ean th\'edch. Y\'eau m\u7897 t t\'ecnh y\'eau v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7891 i \u273 \'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u432 a bao gi\u7901  d\'e1m bi\u7875 u l\u7897  ra, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n cho b\u7843 n th\'e2n bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "Ta bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i, ta s\u7869  \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i qu\'ean nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n v\u7873  ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao c\'f2n c\'f3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, d\'f9 sao c\'f2n nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i m\'e0 em th\'edch, d\'f9 sao c\u7843  hai kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng l\'e0m "B\u7841 n" c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i. Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean l\'e0m b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u, sau \u273 \'f3 l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i th\u7849 m th\u7845 u. . . D\u7851 u c\'f3 th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 n\'f3i, t\u432 \u417 ng lai v\u7851 n r\u7845 t s\'e1ng s\u7911 a. D\'f9 em c\'f3 t\u7841 m th\u7901 i qu\'ean ta, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec. Em v\u7851 n s\u7869  y\'eau ta, em ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  y\'eau ta.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u432 a tay xoa m\'f4i \'e1i nh\'e2n, \'e1nh m\u7855 t t\u297 nh m\u7883 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f4i m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7899 p kh\u259 n \u273 en d\u7847 n \u7843 m \u273 \u7841 m, trong ng\u7921 c \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tr\'e0n l\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c chua x\'f3t kh\'f3 n\'f3i n\'ean l\u7901 i\'97\'97 qu\u7843  nhi\'ean, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c m\'e0 n\'f3i, h\u7855 n c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng b\u7853 n t\'e2m vi\u7879 c m\'ecnh s\u7869  qu\'ean m\u7845 t h\u7855 n. M\'ecnh ch\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t m\'f3n \u259 n ngon m\'e0 th\'f4i. Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng h\'fat m\'e1u tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p t\u7915  c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 l\u7847 n m\u7897 t t\u7913 c s\u7869  c\'f3 l\u7847 n hai, c\'f3 hai th\'ec c\'f3 ba, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng v\u7873  sau h\u7855 n c\'f2n s\u7869  c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng m\'f3n ngon h\u417 n, cho \u273 \u7871 n khi qu\'ean h\u7871 t t\u432  v\u7883  m\'f3n \u259 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ta kh\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7899  r\'f5 ng\u432 \u417 i, ng\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  r\'f5 ta, r\u7845 t c\'f4ng b\u7857 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\u432  c\'e1ch o\'e1n tr\'e1ch. \u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\'e0o ph\'f3ng cho c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n, l\'e0 c\u7853 u ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng y\'eau c\u7847 u qu\'ean \u273 i \'97\'97 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7897 c chi\u7871 m, kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng qu\'ean m\u7845 t, kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, tay \u273 \'e8 ch\u7863 t hoa v\u259 n tr\'ean gh\u7871 , c\u7889  k\'ecm xu\u7889 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng. C\u7853 u tr\u7903  m\'ecnh, \u273 \u432 a tay \'f4m c\u7893  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n nh\u7865  l\'ean h\u7847 u k\u7871  h\u7855 n, n\u7903  m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7907 t nh\u7841 t: "\u272 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , trong ba ng\'e0y n\'e0y, t\'f4i l\'e0 c\u7911 a ng\'e0i. . . T\'f4i thu\u7897 c v\u7873  ng\'e0i, t\u7845 t c\u7843 , \u273 \u7873 u thu\u7897 c v\u7873  ng\'e0i. . ."\cb1 \
