\cf2 \cb3 L\'fac t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang \u7903  trong m\u7897 t kh\'f4ng gian t\u7889 i nh\u432  b\u432 ng, k\'edn m\'edt. Kh\'f4ng gian kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, ho\'e0n to\'e0n phong b\u7871 , b\u7889 n ph\'eda \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i ng\u259 n c\'e1ch, nh\u432 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'f2ng ch\u7843 y kh\'f4ng kh\'ed l\u432 u th\'f4ng, h\'f4 h\u7845 p kh\'f4ng kh\'f3 kh\u259 n, cho n\'ean c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7883  b\u7883 t k\'edn, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u t\'e2m l\'fd v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\'f9 t\'fang kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'ecnh nh\uc0\u432  c\u7853 u... b\u7883  giam trong m\u7897 t c\u7895  quan t\'e0i?\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t c\'e1nh tay kho\'e1c l\'ean ngang h\'f4ng c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'ean tr\'e1i c\u7853 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang n\u7857 m, m\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" to\'e0n th\'e2n l\u7841 nh nh\u432  b\u259 ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nh\u7883 p tim.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ngh\u297  t\u7899 i truy\u7879 n c\u7893  t\'edch *"L\'e3o r\'e2u xanh".\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang ch\u417 i m\u7897 t tr\'f2 ch\u417 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, v\u7915 a d\'f9ng th\'e2n ph\u7853 n th\u7907  s\u259 n cung c\u7845 p tin t\u7913 c cho c\u7853 u, tranh th\u7911  s\u7921  t\'edn nhi\u7879 m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, v\u7915 a d\'f9ng th\'e2n ph\u7853 n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  b\u7913 c b\'e1ch c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t \u273 i v\'e0o b\u7851 y. N\u7871 u c\u7853 u th\'e0nh th\'e0nh th\u7853 t th\u7853 t m\'e0 ch\u417 i c\'f9ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, v\u7853 y th\'ec d\u7877  r\u7891 i, tr\'f2 ch\u417 i ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t, \u273 \'e0o tho\'e1t th\'e0nh c\'f4ng; nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u c\u7853 u qu\'e1 hi\u7871 u k\u7923 , nh\u7845 t nh\u7845 t mu\u7889 n v\u7841 ch tr\u7847 n ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng tr\'f2 ch\u417 i, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u s\u7869  l\u7845 y m\u7841 ng c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean hi\uc0\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u l\'e0 b\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer nh\u7889 t trong quan t\'e0i ch\u7901  ch\u7871 t? V\u7883  b\'ean c\u7841 nh ch\'ednh l\'e0 ti\u7873 n b\u7889 i ch\u7871 t b\u7903 i v\'ec nguy\'ean nh\'e2n t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7849 n th\u7853 n \u273 \u7863 t tay m\'ecnh l\'ean c\'e1nh tay kia, \u273 \u7883 nh tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u273 \u7849 y n\'f3 xu\u7889 ng. B\u7845 t k\u7875  th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 n\'f3i, cho d\'f9 \u273 \u7891 ng b\u7879 nh t\u432 \u417 ng li\'ean, trong m\u7897 t c\u7895  quan t\'e0i b\u7883  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t \'f4m v\u7851 n r\u7845 t kinh h\'e3i. \cb1 \
\
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7849 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1nh tay kia xu\u7889 ng, thi th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'e0ng d\'f9ng s\u7913 c \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n l\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u, gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i kh\'e0n kh\'e0n m\'e0 l\u7847 m b\u7847 m: "Ngoan, b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, b\u7891 i ta m\u7897 t l\'e1t n\u7919 a th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i c\uc0\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901 . C\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c n\'ean x\u432 ng h\'f4 v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o. Do d\u7921  m\u7897 t l\'e1t, c\u7853 u th\u7917  m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "... Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n. Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ch\'ednh l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'e0 h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t ti\u7871 ng Trung, l\u7841 i l\u7915 a m\'ecnh n\'f3i ti\u7871 ng Anh v\u7899 i h\u7855 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng. Th\u7853 t s\u7921  ng\u7851 m l\u7841 i li\u7873 n t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed trong l\'fac nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i t\u7913 c \u273 \u7871 n qu\'ean c\u7843  s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh th\u7853 t kh\u7901 , r\'f5 r\'e0ng ngay t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean m\u417  th\u7845 y gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng kia b\u7903 i v\'ec v\'f4 t\'ecnh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay, \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng trong m\u7897 ng c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 c\'e1nh tay m\u417  h\u7891  tr\u7855 ng nh\u7907 t \u273 \'f3; sau khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'ec m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u tr\u7903  n\'ean r\'f5 r\'e0ng, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3 sai sai khi b\u7903 i v\'ec tay qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i trong m\u7897 ng c\u361 ng theo \u273 \'f3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'97\'97b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n ra hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u259 n b\u7843 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 cho c\u7853 u c\'e2u tr\u7843  l\u7901 i qua nh\u7919 ng gi\u7845 c m\u417  t\u7915  r\u7845 t s\u7899 m, ch\'ednh c\u7853 u l\u7841 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n ch\u7859 ng h\u7873  hay bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , nh\u7851 n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u7851 n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 \u273 \u7849 y ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh h\u7887 i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i m\u417  r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u v\u7873  ng\'e0i, \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 do ng\'e0i l\'e0m sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u nh\u432  t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 s\u7921  s\u7855 p x\u7871 p t\'ednh to\'e1n c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng... C\u7853 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, v\u7853 y th\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 , kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c mu\u7889 n \u273 \'f9a gi\u7905 n m\'ecnh \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c n\'e0o. \cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i ta." Trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'e2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean kh\u7869  h\'f4n m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, "B\u7843 o b\u7889 i, kh\'f4ng n\'ean nghi th\u7847 n nghi qu\u7927  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 \'f3 ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 ng c\u7911 a em th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat h\u7855 n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng b\u7893  sung: "Nh\u432 ng chuy\u7879 n ph\'e1t sinh \u7903  ch\u7895  ta \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\u7897 ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i em th\u7845 y th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 ta. Em ngon mi\u7879 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y nh\'e0o t\u7899 i c\u7885  ta, ta c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c." N\'f3i xong l\u7901 i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng, trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n nhi\u7873 u th\'eam ch\'fat \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i tri\u7873 n mi\'ean l\u432 u luy\u7871 n. \cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7895 n \u273 \u7843 n. V\'f4 s\u7881  h\u7895 n \u273 \u7843 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7863 t n\'f3ng l\'ean t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7907 t, ph\'e1t nhi\u7879 t, c\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u \u273 i, kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n l\u7841 i nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n m\'ea luy\u7871 n Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer, c\u361 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  tin t\u432 \u7903 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\u7915  n\u7897 i t\'e2m, b\u7843 n n\u259 ng m\'e0 tin c\u7853 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. Nh\u432 ng s\u7921  th\u7853 t ch\u7913 ng minh th\'e2n ph\u7853 n th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ngay t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t tr\'f2 l\u7915 a b\u7883 p. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m y\'eau c\u7847 u xa v\u7901 i chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c, ch\u7881  hy v\u7885 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  b\'ecnh y\'ean v\'f4 s\u7921  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i v\u7883  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "R\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c ng\'e0i mu\u7889 n g\'ec?" C\u7853 u h\u7887 i th\u7859 ng, "Mu\u7889 n h\'fat m\'e1u hay g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, n\u7871 u ba ng\'e0y kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911  th\'ec ba m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y, t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  thu\u7897 c v\u7873  ng\'e0i, ho\'e0n to\'e0n th\u7887 a m\'e3n t\u7845 t c\u7843  nhu c\u7847 u c\u7911 a ng\'e0i, ng\'e0i mu\u7889 n \u273 \'f9a gi\u7905 n th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng c\u7853 u tho\'e1ng ngh\u7865 n: "Nh\u432 ng l\u7847 n n\'e0y ng\'e0i \u273 \u7915 ng g\u7841 t t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng, sau khi \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t th\'ec d\u7913 t kho\'e1t th\u7843  t\'f4i \u273 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c ph\'fat ch\u7889 c, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "A Di\'ean, em \u273 ang gi\u7853 n ta sao? Ta th\u7873  v\u7899 i tr\u7901 i, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  vi\u7879 c kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927 , nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i ta t\u7915 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i em kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t c\'e2u l\'e0 gi\u7843 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i c\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  vi\u7879 c m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u th\u7873  v\u7899 i tr\u7901 i th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n l\u7853 t c\u7853 u l\u7841 i, \'f4m tr\u7885 n v\'e0o ng\u7921 c: "Th\u7853 t \u273 \u7845 y. M\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u ta c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n g\u7841 t em, l\'e0 em n\'f3i em c\u259 m gh\'e9t ta, gh\'e9t ta h\'fat m\'e1u em, ta kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n em s\u7907  h\'e3i tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh n\'ean m\u7899 i gi\u7843  l\'e0m th\u7907  s\u259 n qu\u7927 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em gh\'e9t ta h\'fat m\'e1u em, v\uc0\u7853 y em u\u7889 ng m\'e1u ta \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? L\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c em c\'f2n r\u7845 t th\'edch u\u7889 ng m\'e1u c\u7911 a ta m\'e0. A Di\'ean, \u273 \u7915 ng gi\u7853 n ta, l\'e0 ta sai r\u7891 i, em mu\u7889 n ta l\'e0m g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 \u7915 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y." H\u7855 n n\'f3i xong li\u7873 n mu\u7889 n \u273 \u432 a c\u7893  tay t\u7899 i b\'ean mi\u7879 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ho\'e0n to\'e0n qu\'ean r\u7857 ng v\u7899 i kh\u7843  n\u259 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\u7855 n r\'e1ch n\u7893 i da h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng mu\uc0\u7889 n." Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u tr\'e1nh kh\u7887 i, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i th\'eam g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng \u273 o\'e1n ra t\'e2m t\u432  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, ngh\u297  c\'e1ch mu\u7889 n l\'e0m c\u7853 u vui, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean n\'f3i g\'ec, suy ngh\u297  ch\u7889 c l\'e1t th\u7917  h\u7887 i: "Chi\u7871 c quan t\'e0i n\'e0y em c\'f3 th\'edch kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tho\u7843 i m\'e1i kh\'f4ng? \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 quan t\'e0i c\u7911 a ta, nh\u7919 ng con qu\u7927  kh\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u mu\u7889 n m\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, sau n\'e0y ch\'fang ta s\u7869  c\'f9ng \u7903  trong n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng r\'f5 v\uc0\u7883  Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng n\u259 m l\u7847 n b\u7843 y l\u432 \u7907 t \u273 \u7893 i tr\'f2 b\u7883 p b\u7907 m \u273 \'f9a b\u7905 n m\'ecnh t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i, b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\u7841 i c\u432  x\u7917  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n c\'f9ng l\'e0 mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u7903  l\u7841 i trong chi\u7871 c quan t\'e0i n\'e0y th\'eam n\u7919 a, b\'e8n nh\'e2n c\u417  h\u7897 i n\'f3i: "T\u7889 i qu\'e1, t\'f4i mu\u7889 n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i. Ng\'e0i \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i ra ngo\'e0i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n l\'e0 ng\u7919  kh\'ed cung k\'ednh m\'e0 xa c\'e1ch, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n xa c\'e1ch h\u417 n so v\u7899 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7853 u \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 ch\'fat lu\u7889 ng cu\u7889 ng, h\u7855 n th\'e0 r\u7857 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'e1ch m\u7855 ng h\u7855 n ho\u7863 c d\'f9ng c\'e1ch g\'ec tr\u7915 ng ph\u7841 t h\u7855 n c\u361 ng t\u7889 t h\u417 n so v\u7899 i hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i. \'c1i nh\'e2n nh\u432  v\u7853 y khi\u7871 n h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao. \cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n mu\u7889 n c\u7913 ng r\u7855 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  "Em kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n \u7903  c\'f9ng ta th\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u7915 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c ra kh\u7887 i quan t\'e0i", nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n v\u7915 a kh\'f4ng n\u7905  v\u7915 a kh\'f4ng d\'e1m; h\u7855 n ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  thu\u7853 n theo t\'e2m \'fd c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tr\'e1i n\u7917 a ph\u7847 n. Sau khi nghe v\u7853 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7897 i v\'e0ng l\u7845 y l\'f2ng m\'e0 \'f4m l\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7909 c c\u432 ng c\u7911 a ta kh\'f4ng n\'ean t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n n\u7919 a, l\'e3o c\'f4ng mang em ra ngo\'e0i. N\u7871 u em kh\'f4ng th\'edch th\'ec v\u7873  sau ch\'fang ta ng\u7911  gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t h\u7855 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  mu\u7889 n mang theo Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng ng\u7911  trong quan t\'e0i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7889  \'fd mu\u7889 n d\u7885 a ng\u432 \u7901 i. B\u7843 n th\'e2n l\'e0 Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, s\u7903  th\'edch \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i quan t\'e0i truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i ch\u7881  x\u7871 p th\u7913  hai, h\u7855 n th\'edch c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u7875  \'e1i nh\'e2n b\'ean c\u7841 nh h\u417 n, \u7903  trong kh\'f4ng gian nh\u7887  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, ch\u7881  c\'f3 l\u7851 n nhau, kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\u7913  g\'ec kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u7911  quan t\'e0i r\u7845 t \u7845 m \'e1p, \'e1i nh\'e2n kh\'f4ng th\'edch, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng ng\'e0y th\'e1ng sau n\'e0y c\'f2n d\'e0i, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean v\u7851 n s\u7869  c\'f3 d\u7883 p \u273 \u7875  A Di\'ean c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n s\u7921  tuy\u7879 t di\u7879 u l\'fac ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i trong quan t\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7849 y v\'e1n quan t\'e0i ra, \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i. Quan t\'e0i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n cao h\u417 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7889 n v\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u417 n nh\u7861 n, h\u7855 n lo l\u7855 ng \'e1i nh\'e2n leo ra s\u7869  g\u7863 p kh\'f3 kh\u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7843  xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh xung quanh, m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t v\'e0 b\u7889 n v\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u b\u7857 ng \u273 \'e1, tr\'ean t\u7845 t c\u7843  v\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u treo ch\'e2n n\u7871 n s\u7855 t, ph\'eda tr\'ean th\u7855 p n\u7871 n m\'e0u cam. Kh\'f4ng gian n\u417 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c quan t\'e0i \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng b\u7857 ng g\u7895 , b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7873 m \u273 \'e1 u\u7889 n l\u432 \u7907 n h\u432 \u7899 ng l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\uc0\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 l\u7841 i quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn mi\u7879 ng chi\u7871 c quan t\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en trang nghi\'eam kia, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 n\u7857 m \u7903  \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  ch\u7881  th\u7873 m \u273 \'e1: "Ch\'fang ta \u273 ang \u7903  d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, n\u417 i n\'e0y th\'f4ng th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u7911 a ta, nh\u432 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 i h\u417 n m\u7897 t tr\u259 m b\u7853 c thang."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u7849 n th\u7853 n nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "A Di\'ean, ta \'f4m em l\'ean nh\'e9?" Trong m\u7855 t h\u7855 n nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7873 m \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c ni\u7871 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i l\'e0 v\u7905 , kh\u7893 ng t\u432 \u7899 c l\'e0 h\u7855 n hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i qu\u7843  th\u7921 c kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n bu\'f4ng tha b\u7845 t k\u7923  c\u417  h\u7897 i xun xoe n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n, c\'e1m \u417 n ng\'e0i, t\'f4i t\u7921  \u273 i l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c." Tuy r\u7857 ng t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i sau h\'f4n m\'ea c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7851 n h\u417 i v\'f4 l\u7921 c, nh\u432 ng leo c\u7847 u thang th\'ec kh\'f4ng v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7921 c s\u7921  kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng \u273 ang di\u7877 n vai g\'ec, t\u7921  g\u7885 i m\'ecnh l\'e0 l\'e3o c\'f4ng m\'e0 c\u361 ng quen mi\u7879 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 v\'f4 c\'f9ng \'e2n c\u7847 n, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  l\'fac \u7903  trong m\u7897 ng bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 l\u7845 y l\'f2ng v\u7883  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0y, khi\u7871 n h\u7855 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7913 ng th\'fa, cho n\'ean sau vai "Th\u7907  s\u259 n g\'e0 m\u7901  th\'e2n thi\u7879 n" \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh "L\'e3o c\'f4ng nh\u7883  th\u7853 p t\u7913  hi\u7871 u v\'e0 ti\u7875 u ki\u7873 u th\'ea" ? M\'ecnh c\'f3 n\'ean di\u7877 n c\'f9ng h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng? N\u7871 u m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng ph\u7889 i h\u7907 p th\'ec li\u7879 u h\u7855 n c\'f3 tr\u7903  m\u7863 t gi\u7871 t m\'ecnh lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ngh\u297  ng\u7907 i lung tung nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 i l\'ean c\u7847 u thang, c\u7917 a ra l\'e0 m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  r\u7845 t r\u7897 ng, b\u7889  tr\'ed r\u7845 t gi\u7889 ng v\u7899 i c\u259 n ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y "Trong m\u417 ", trang tr\'ed r\u7845 t \'edt, ch\u7881  \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n \u273 \u7863 t t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, gi\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7911 , t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\'e0 l\'f2 s\u432 \u7903 i \'e2m t\u432 \u7901 ng, cho n\'ean kh\'f4ng gian c\'e0ng th\'eam tr\u7889 ng. Tr\'ean t\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 hai c\u7917 a s\u7893  nh\u7887 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u \'e1nh s\'e1ng xuy\'ean qua l\'e0m trong ph\'f2ng c\'e0ng th\'eam \'e2m u l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7855 t c\u7853 u ra kh\u7887 i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , \u273 i tham quan n\u417 i kh\'e1c: "N\u417 i n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 t\u7915  r\u7845 t l\'e2u, b\u7889  c\u7909 c v\'e0 ki\u7871 n tr\'fac \u273 \u7873 u t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i c\u361 , ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  n\'e0y l\'e0 v\u7873  sau ta cho x\'e2y th\'eam, nh\u7919 ng ch\u7895  kh\'e1c ch\u432 a h\u7873  thay \u273 \u7893 i, h\u7857 ng n\u259 m ch\u7881  tu s\u7917 a theo th\'f4ng l\u7879 , sau n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  b\'e0i tr\'ed s\u7917 a l\u7841 i theo s\u7903  th\'edch c\u7911 a em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u d\u7855 t \u273 i d\u7841 o to\'e0n b\u7897  l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i. Qu\u7843  nhi\'ean \u273 \'fang nh\u432  l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u7903  n\u417 i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 di\u7879 n t\'edch nh\u7887  h\u7865 p, h\u417 n n\u7919 a to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7875  \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7911  nh\'e2n kh\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i n\'e0y, m\'e0 trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i c\u361 ng r\u7845 t \'edt c\'f3 kh\'e1ch t\u7899 i th\u259 m.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7851 n c\u7853 u ra ngo\'e0i l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i, \u273 i ra s\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong hoa vi\'ean xum xu\'ea l\'e1 c\'e2y m\'e0u xanh \uc0\u273 \u7853 m \u273 \'e3 tho\'e1ng th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng b\'fap hoa tr\u7855 ng lay \u273 \u7897 ng trong gi\'f3 nh\u7865 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i xa v\'e0i b\u432 \u7899 c nh\'ecn l\u7841 i t\'f2a l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 ban ng\'e0y, t\'f2a l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en trang nghi\'eam d\u432 \u7899 i tr\u7901 i xanh, hai \u273 \u7881 nh th\'e1p hai b\'ean tr\u7921 c ch\u7881  l\'ean tr\u7901 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  k\u7925  s\u297  \u273 en trong c\u7901  vua. C\u7853 u li\u7871 c m\u7855 t li\u7873 n nh\u7853 n ra t\'f2a l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\'f2a l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i c\u7893  trong \u7843 nh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 g\u7917 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c. L\'fac \u7845 y c\u7853 u c\'f2n l\u417  \u273 \u7877 nh n\'f3i v\u7873  sau c\'f3 c\u417  h\u7897 i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3 ng\u7855 m, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  r\u7857 ng m\u7897 t c\'e2u th\'e0nh th\u7853 t, ch\u7911  nh\'e2n th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \'e3 mang c\u7853 u t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 y th\'ec nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i l\'fac \u7845 y x\'e1c th\u7921 c \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 n\'f3i th\u7853 t, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7889  \'fd khoe khoang kho\'e1c l\'e1c. D\'f9 sao... h\u7855 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. \cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i nhanh v\'e0i b\u432 \u7899 c \u273 u\u7893 i theo c\u7853 u: "Ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n th\u7901 i gian ta \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, l\'fac \u7845 y em c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i em th\'edch ch\u7895  n\'e0y, v\u7853 y n\'ean ta mang em t\u7899 i n\u417 i n\'e0y. N\u7871 u em kh\'f4ng th\'edch ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'f4\u777 i n\u417 i kh\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "Nh\u432 ng hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i t\'f4i ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n tr\u7903  v\u7873 , t\'f4i ph\u7843 i quay v\u7873  h\u7885 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u ng\u432 ng m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Xin l\u7895 i, A Di\'ean, t\u7841 m th\u7901 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 vi\u7879 c n\'e0y kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac c\'f3 th\u7875  x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c em, ta s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng bu\'f4ng tay em."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Chuy\uc0\u7879 n \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng ta s\u7869  xin ngh\u7881  ph\'e9p cho em, em c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'ean m\u7841 ng h\u7885 c qua gi\'e1o tr\'ecnh video, c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  trao \u273 \u7893 i v\u7899 i c\'e1c b\u7841 n qua m\u7841 ng, n\u7897 p b\'e0i t\u7853 p. N\u7871 u em v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nh\u432  v\u7853 y b\u7845 t l\u7907 i v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c h\u7885 c, ta c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7901 i gi\'e1o s\u432  chuy\'ean ng\'e0nh tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \u7871 n l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i d\u7841 y em." Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c b\u7893  sung, "Ta s\u7869  t\u7853 n l\u7921 c kh\'f4ng gi\u7899 i h\u7841 n em, c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m tr\u7877  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n c\u7911 a em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7907  h\u7871 t h\u7891 n. Tuy r\u7857 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  gi\'e1o s\u432  c\'e1c tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c n\u7893 i danh qu\u7889 c t\u7871  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 th\u7901 i gian qu\'fd gi\'e1 c\u7921 c k\u7923  kh\'f3 th\u7881 nh, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u tin t\u432 \u7903 ng chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m kh\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7883  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  n\'e0y. \cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\u7855 t v\'e0o trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i giam l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7911  \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  r\u7891 i, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n b\u7883  nh\u7889 t trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i n\u7841 p ki\u7871 n th\u7913 c chuy\'ean ng\'e0nh m\u7895 i ng\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\'fat ngh\uc0\u297  ng\u7907 i c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t: "C\u7843 m \u417 n ng\'e0i, vi\u7879 c n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0... ng\'e0i c\'f3 th\u7875  ngh\u297  c\'e1ch mi\u7877 n tr\u7915  t\u7845 t c\u7843  b\'e0i t\u7853 p trong ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh h\u7885 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\
