\cf2 \cb3 Trong l\'e2u \uc0\u273 \'e0i c\u7911 a Emmer, t\u7845 t c\u7843  Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c t\'f4i t\u7899  \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra khi n\'e0o Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  h\u7841 nh ph\'fac v\'e0 \u432 u th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n v\uc0\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i nh\u432  th\u7871 . Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia h\u7855 n v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u7843 m x\'fac, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u l\'e3nh l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m \u273 \u7841 m, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m nh\'e0m ch\'e1n s\u7869  v\'e0o quan t\'e0i ng\u7911 , m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c ng\u7911  ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7845 y tr\u259 m n\u259 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  l\u7847 n n\'e0y, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 tr\u7885 n v\u7865 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  trong quan t\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7885 i thay \u273 \u7893 i n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 v\'ec nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i h\u7855 n mang v\u7873  kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'e2u \uc0\u273 \'e0i t\u7845 t c\u7843  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c: th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \'f4m nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i h\'fat m\'e1u ng\u7911 , th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m m\u7895 i l\u7847 n nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i kia n\'f3i "Kh\'f4ng \u273 \'f3i kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u259 n, \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i tr\u7903  v\u7873  n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng t\'f4i s\u7869  tuy\u7879 t th\u7921 c, ng\'e0i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\'e1u ngon \u273 \u7875  u\u7889 ng \u273 \'e2u, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7847 n n\'e0y t\'f4i th\u7853 t s\u7921  nghi\'eam t\'fac \u273 \u7845 y, ng\'e0i c\u432 \u7905 ng \'e9p mang t\'f4i \u273 i ph\'f2ng \u259 n c\u361 ng v\'f4 d\u7909 ng", nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  c\u7847 n ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n \u259 n cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n ngoan ngo\'e3n \u259 n h\u7871 t s\u7841 ch \u273 \u7891  \u259 n h\u7855 n t\u7921  tay l\'e0m; m\u7895 i l\u7847 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  \u273 \u7873 u t\u7887  ra h\u7841 nh ph\'fac vui m\u7915 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng. Nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 gi\u7853 n d\u7895 i kh\'f4ng vui s\u7869  l\'e0m \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y phi\u7873 n n\'e3o \u432 u th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Alberta ph\uc0\u7909  tr\'e1ch ph\u7847 n h\u7853 u c\u7847 n y\'ean l\u7863 ng nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng ngh\u7883  lu\u7853 n c\'f9ng qu\u7843 n gia ti\'ean sinh: "Th\u7913  cho ta n\'f3i th\u7859 ng, ta kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ra v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  mang v\u7873  c\'f3 ch\u7895  n\'e0o kh\'f4ng vui, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng th\'edch Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  n\'e0y c\u361 ng l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \'e3 s\u7889 ng h\u417 n m\u7897 t ngh\'ecn n\u259 m, t\u7921  nh\u7853 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 th\u7875  nghi\u7879 m v\'e0 quan s\'e1t t\u7881  m\u7881  c\u7843 m x\'fac c\u7911 a con ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7921 c k\'ec m\u7851 n c\u7843 m. Theo nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m quan s\'e1t c\u7911 a b\'e0, kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7911  chung v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh gh\'e9t m\u7895 i ng\'e0y m\'e0 c\'f2n h\'e0ng \u273 \'eam an gi\u7845 c ng\u7911  say, kh\'f4ng ai ng\'e0y ng\'e0y c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh gh\'e9t \u259 n chung m\'e0 c\'f2n \u259 n ng\'e0y c\'e0ng ngon mi\u7879 ng. Ng\u432 \u417 i c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7903 i v\'ec gh\'e9t m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  \'fd ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ng\u432 \u417 i th\'edch m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i s\u7869  v\'f4 th\u7913 c v\'e2y quanh ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 v\uc0\u7883  ti\'ean sinh nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i n\'e0y r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p sau, b\u7857 ng ch\u7913 ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 khi c\u7853 u ta \u7903  c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895  v\u7899 i Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , t\u7847 m m\u7855 t c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  chung quy s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 d\'ednh v\'e0o nhau, \'e1nh m\u7855 t d\'e2y d\u432 a l\u7851 n nhau, nh\u432 ng ai c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i m\u7897 t l\u7901 i. M\'e3i cho \u273 \u7871 n khi \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y \'f4m nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , b\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed im l\u7863 ng l\u7841 i tri\u7873 n mi\'ean \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  ph\'e1 v\u7905 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e2n lo\uc0\u7841 i kia ch\u7881  m\u7899 i s\u7889 ng h\u417 n hai m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m non n\u7899 t, \u7903  trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u t\u7913  c\u7889  v\'f4 th\'e2n, \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" th\'e2n nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\'ean \u273 \u7847 u s\u7887  b\u7855 t c\u7853 u ta v\u7873 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed ngay c\u7843  khi c\u7889  g\u7855 ng t\u7887  ra \u273 \u7841 m m\u7841 c xa c\'e1ch c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng duy tr\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\'e1 ba ng\'e0y. Alberta th\'f4ng hi\u7875 u t\'e2m l\'fd m\u7897 t m\u7863 t c\u7843 m th\'e1n sau l\u432 ng, n\'f3i c\u7853 u: "Qu\u7843  th\u7921 c \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng nh\u432  c\'f4 d\'e2u lo\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u432 \u7905 ng \'e9p c\u432 \u7899 p v\u7873  nh\u7889 t trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i ", m\u7897 t m\u7863 t l\u7841 i s\u7861 n l\'f2ng m\'e0 ti\u7871 p tay cho t\u7897 i \'e1c c\u7911 a \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , mong m\u7887 i \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7899 m l\'e0m ti\u7875 u b\u7843 o b\u7889 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh vui v\u7867 . Ph\u7843 i bi\u7871 t r\u7857 ng ngh\'ecn n\u259 m qua, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  mang ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i v\u7873  l\'e3nh th\u7893  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, c\u361 ng th\u7875  hi\u7879 n ra t\'ecnh c\u7843 m kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  che gi\u7845 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'e2u \uc0\u273 \'e0i t\u7845 t c\u7843  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u t\'f4i t\u7899  \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 t ti\u7875 u nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh tho\'e1t kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i tay \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , \u273 \'e2y ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  th\u7901 i gian s\u7899 m mu\u7897 n. Nh\u432 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i ch\u7881  gi\u7919  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7887 n v\u7865 n b\u7889 n ng\'e0y \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n th\u7845 t th\u7911 , bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i ng\'e0y th\u7913  n\u259 m \u273 \'e3 m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a b\u7883  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  tri\u7879 t tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7875  m\'e0 \u259 n v\'e0o b\u7909 ng -- Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7883 nh che gi\u7845 u \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y, tr\'ean th\u7921 c t\u7871  h\u7855 n l\'e0m ra \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh r\u7845 t l\u7899 n. Tuy r\u7857 ng trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i \u273 \'e1m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u gi\u7843  v\u7901  l\'e0m vi\u7879 c ch\u259 m ch\u7881 , kh\'f4ng li\u7871 c ngang li\u7871 c d\u7885 c kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m \u273 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng ri\'eang t\u432  c\u7911 a ch\u7911  nh\'e2n, nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e2y v\u7851 n l\'e0 tin t\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c truy\u7873 n \u273 i nhanh nh\u7845 t kh\u7855 p l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 n n\u7919 a b\u7885 n c\'f2n bi\u7871 t, t\u7915  ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 tr\u7903  \u273 i, \u273 \u7841 i ti\u7879 c c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng gi\'e1n \u273 o\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean ban ng\'e0y khi tr\'f4ng th\uc0\u7845 y nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i l\u7841 i \u273 ang g\'e2y chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 th\u7903  d\'e0i, nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i, th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 lo\'e0i sinh v\u7853 t \'fd ch\'ed kh\'f4ng ki\'ean \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7841 i th\'edch l\u7915 a m\'ecnh d\u7889 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Alberta h\uc0\u7887 i qu\u7843 n gia ti\'ean sinh: "Grey, ta ngh\u297  li\u7879 u ch\'fang ta c\'f3 n\'ean chu\u7849 n b\u7883  h\'f4n l\u7877  kh\'f4ng? Chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y n\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chu\u7849 n b\u7883  s\u7899 m m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \'edt nh\u7845 t ph\u7843 i n\u7917 a n\u259 m, ph\u7843 i l\'ean danh s\'e1ch kh\'e1ch m\u7901 i r\u7891 i c\'f2n g\u7917 i thi\u7879 p m\u7901 i. H\'f4n l\u7877  c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7841 i s\u7921 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey tr\uc0\u7847 m ng\'e2m hai gi\'e2y, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "V\u7853 y th\'ec b\u7855 t tay chu\u7849 n b\u7883  th\'f4i, l\'e0m phi\u7873 n b\'e0 r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n kh\'f4ng th\'e8m \u273 i xin ch\u7881  th\u7883  t\u7915  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey th\uc0\u7847 m ngh\u297 , h\'f4n l\u7877  n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0m l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, d\'f9 sao \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c mu\u7889 n m\u7901 i ai \u273 \u7871 n d\u7921  l\u7877 . V\u7873  ph\u7847 n ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n b\u7841 n b\'e8 c\u7911 a V\u432 \u417 ng phi \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7901 i th\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'ednh sau, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'f2n ph\u7843 i m\u432 \u7907 n \u273 \u7897 i ch\u7845 p ph\'e1p \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m b\u7843 o v\u7879 . \u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng vi\u7879 c b\u7889  tr\'ed h\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng, l\u7877  ph\u7909 c, d\'e1ng nh\u7851 n, lo\u7841 i hoa v\u7851 n s\u7869  do \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  t\u7921  m\'ecnh quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng n\'f3i nh\uc0\u7919 ng suy ngh\u297  n\'e0y v\u7899 i Alberta, b\'e0 li\'ean t\u7909 c t\'e1n d\u432 \u417 ng: "\'d4ng \u273 \'fang l\'e0 m\u7897 t v\u7883  qu\u7843 n gia chu \u273 \'e1o, s\u7855 p x\u7871 p m\u7885 i vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7873 u chu to\'e0n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey khi\'eam t\uc0\u7889 n m\'e0 \u273 \'e1p: "Nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 vi\u7879 c t\'f4i n\'ean l\'e0m, tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m t\u7893  ch\u7913 c h\'f4n l\u7877 , c\'f2n c\u7847 n b\'e0 ch\u7881  b\u7843 o nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7859 ng h\u7873  hay bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\u7855 t tay v\'e0o an b\'e0i h\'f4n l\u7877  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, c\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n kh\'f4ng r\'f5 trong t\'f2a l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau t\'f4i t\u7899  qu\u7927 . B\u7903 i v\'ec m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n \u273 \u7873 u b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u l\'e0m vi\u7879 c v\'e0o ban \u273 \'eam, qu\'e9t d\u7885 n l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i, ch\u259 m s\'f3c v\u432 \u7901 n hoa, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  nguy\'ean li\u7879 u n\u7845 u \u259 n... Nh\u7919 ng c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u ho\'e0n th\'e0nh trong \u273 \'eam, m\'e0 l\'fac \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 . Ban ng\'e0y \u273 a s\u7889  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i m\u7897 t v\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m "Ca ng\'e0y" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean th\uc0\u7921 c t\u7871  b\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u259 ng r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u th\u7901 i gian ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng ban ng\'e0y, ho\'e0n to\'e0n bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh r\u7891 i m\u7897 t qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u "Ng\'e0y \u273 \'eam \u273 \u7843 o l\u7897 n", \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m h\'e0i l\'f2ng y\'eau c\u7847 u c\u7911 a ch\u7911  nh\'e2n, Grey \u273 \'e3 an b\'e0i th\'eam qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\'e0m vi\u7879 c ban ng\'e0y, c\u361 ng t\u259 ng th\'eam tr\u7907  c\u7845 p "Ca ng\'e0y" cho b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 S\'e1ng nay, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u432  m\u7885 i khi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i trong v\'f2ng tay Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, c\u7853 u kh\u7869  nheo nheo m\u7855 t, l\u7841 i nh\u7855 m l\u7841 i, l\u417  m\u417  m\'e0 \u273 \u7849 y ng\u7921 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, m\u7845 y gi\u7901  r\u7891 i, \u273 i l\'e0m b\u7919 a s\'e1ng \u273 i, t\'f4i \u273 \'f3i b\u7909 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 "M\uc0\u7897 t l\'fac n\u7919 a r\u7891 i d\u7853 y." H\u7855 n m\u7903  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn \u273 \u7891 ng h\u7891 , "M\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901  r\u7891 i, b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, ch\'fang ta \u259 n tr\u432 a lu\'f4n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? Nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7911  th\'eam m\u7897 t gi\u7901  n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i xong l\u7841 i k\'e9o ch\u259 n l\'ean ph\u7911  k\'edn hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, \'f4m c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau m\u7873 m m\u7841 i nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 m." Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\u7869  l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, c\u7885  c\u7885  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ng\u7911  ti\u7871 p. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, d\'f9 sao trong m\u7897 t th\'e1ng n\'e0y th\u7901 i gian sinh ho\u7841 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng gi\u7889 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. Th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean l\'e0 gi\u7919 a tr\u432 a m\u7897 t hai gi\u7901  m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u259 n s\'e1ng k\u7871 t h\u7907 p \u259 n tr\u432 a, t\'e1m gi\u7901  t\u7889 i \u259 n t\u7889 i v\'e0 \u259 n khuya, sau \u273 \'f3 c\'f9ng v\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng, li\'ean t\u7909 c qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y nhau, m\'e3i cho \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 a ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau m\u7899 i l\u7841 i th\u7913 c d\u7853 y. Tuy r\u7857 ng sa \u273 \u7885 a l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t cho s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e, nh\u432 ng qu\u7843  th\u7921 c th\'edch \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c hi\u7875 u v\'ec sao c\'f3 t\u7915  "\u258 n ch\u417 i tr\'e1c t\'e1ng", hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u \u273 ang b\u7915 a b\'e3i m\u7895 i ng\'e0y v\u7899 i m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u hay sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng s\u7855 p ng\u7911  ti\u7871 p, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7907 t thanh t\u7881 nh, l\u7841 i h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, h\'f4m nay l\'e0 ng\'e0y bao nhi\'eau?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 m..., " qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, "Ta ngh\u297 ... ch\u7855 c l\'e0 m\'f9ng 6 th\'e1ng 6."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1p \'e1n kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u432 \u417 n tay s\u7901  t\'ecm di \u273 \u7897 ng, m\u7903  ra nh\'ecn -- \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 m\'f9ng b\u7843 y th\'e1ng s\'e1u, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  v\u7883  h\'e1o s\u7855 c b\'ean c\u7841 nh l\'e0m lu m\u7901  \u273 \u7847 u \'f3c, ho\'e0n to\'e0n tr\u7847 m m\'ea trong s\u7921  d\u7883 u d\'e0ng c\u7911 a Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , kh\'f4ng m\'e0ng th\u7871  s\u7921  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t th\u7901 i gian.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7853 t d\u7853 y: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, k\u7923  thi c\u7911 a t\'f4i s\u7855 p \u273 \u7871 n r\u7891 i! T\'f4i nh\u7899  h\'ecnh nh\u432  m\'f4n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean thi ng\'e0y 9 th\'e1ng 6."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng ng\'e0y qua th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 c\'f9ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c b\u7915 a b\'e3i qu\'e1 qu\'e1 m\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec x\u7843 y ra, v\u7889 n \u273 ang v\u7915 a t\u7913 c v\u7915 a s\u7907 , nh\u432 ng ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 sau khi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\u7895 i b\u7919 a \u259 n \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t ngon m\u7895 i ng\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 do qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u t\u7921  tay l\'e0m li\u7873 n x\u7909 i xu\u7889 ng, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i m\u7873 m l\'f2ng, lui m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7887 ... K\u7871 t qu\u7843  v\u7873  sau li\u7873 n b\u7883  con qu\u7927  ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t h\u7841 i n\u432 \u7899 c h\u7841 i d\'e2n n\'e0y n\u7917 a d\u7909  d\u7895  n\u7917 a \'e9p bu\u7897 c m\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n th\'e0nh quan h\u7879  th\'e2n m\u7853 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y. C\u7853 u c\'f2n, c\'f2n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t h\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7909 ... c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u h\u7871 t thu\u7889 c ch\u7919 a r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng? Sau khi b\u7883  giam \u7903  l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i h\'ecnh nh\u432  ch\u7913 ng Stockholm c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\'f2n n\u7863 ng h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh nh\u432  m\u7897 t... thanh ni\'ean kh\'f4ng \'fd ch\'ed..., bi\u7871 t r\'f5 tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c m\u7899 i l\'e0 nh\'e0, h\u7885 c t\u7853 p m\u7899 i l\'e0 ch\'ednh th\'ea, v\u7883  Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7889 t l\'e0nh g\'ec, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\'f2n l\u7915 a g\u7841 t m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\'ea ho\u7863 c, b\u7883  d\u7909  d\u7895  tr\u7885 n v\u7865 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng kh\'f4ng v\u7873  nh\'e0 ng\u7911 , \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ch\'ednh th\'ea l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng. \u272 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  ch\'ednh th\'ea \u273 ang c\u7847 m gia ph\'e1p ch\u7901  \u7903  nh\'e0 th\'ec m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \'e2n h\u7853 n \'96 k\u7923  thi c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng \'f4m l\u7845 y c\u7853 u t\u7915  ph\'eda sau, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n g\'e1y c\u7853 u: "\u272 \u7915 ng g\u7845 p, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, ta c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  cho b\u7885 n h\u7885  mi\u7877 n k\'ec thi c\u7911 a em. Em mu\u7889 n bao nhi\'eau \u273 i\u7875 m?"\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'e0y l\uc0\u7841 i c\'e0ng khinh ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u417 n. \u272 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 ti\u7875 u tam c\'f3 quy\u7873 n c\'f3 th\u7871  coi tr\u7901 i b\u7857 ng vung ch\'e8n \'e9p ch\'ednh th\'ea.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 nh nh\u7841 t n\'f3i: "Ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh h\u7885 c trao \u273 \u7893 i kh\'f4ng t\'ednh th\'e0nh t\'edch, quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng t\'f4i s\u7869  \u273 \u259 ng k\'fd *mi\u7877 n tu, cho n\'ean \u273 \u7841 t ti\'eau chu\u7849 n l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (*mi\uc0\u7877 n tu: c\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o t\'ecnh h\'ecnh h\u7885 c t\u7853 p ho\u7863 c th\'e0nh t\'edch m\'e0 cho ph\'e9p sinh vi\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mi\u7877 n ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh h\u7885 c)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i tr\u7885 ng \u273 i\u7875 m. C\u7853 u quay \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n: "T\'f4i ph\u7843 i quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng thi, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  nguy\'ean t\u7855 c." C\u7853 u ph\u7843 i l\'e0m m\u7897 t tr\u432 \u7907 ng phu bi\u7871 t g\'e1nh v\'e1c c\'f3 tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m, tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e3 chung ch\u7841  v\u7899 i qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u nhi\u7873 u ng\'e0y nh\u432  v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i quay v\u7873  thi, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng d\'f9 cho c\'f3 nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7857 ng th\'ec c\u361 ng th\u7845 y th\u7865 n trong l\'f2ng, b\u7909 ng d\u7841  kh\'f4ng y\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u273 \u7863 t c\u7857 m l\'ean vai c\u7853 u, nh\u7853 n l\u7901 i n\'f3i: "C\'f3 th\u7875 . Ta s\u7869  an b\'e0i m\'e1y bay chi\u7873 u mai \u273 \u432 a em tr\u7903  v\u7873 . Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u, b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, ta c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n em \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng m\u7897 t nguy\u7879 n v\u7885 ng c\u7911 a ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e0 chuy\uc0\u7879 n g\'ec?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'eam nay ng\u7911  trong quan t\'e0i c\'f9ng ta." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  n\'f3i, "C\'f2n c\'f3, \u273 \u7875  ch\'e0o \u273 \'f3n em, l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i \u273 \'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  m\u7897 t b\u7919 a ti\u7879 c, c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'e0 t\u7893  ch\u7913 c t\u7889 i nay, em ph\u7843 i c\'f3 m\u7863 t v\u7899 i t\u432  c\'e1ch l\'e0 b\u7841 n \u273 \u7901 i c\u7911 a ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7915 ng \u273 \u7901 : "... \u272 \u7873 u l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u sao?" C\u7853 u h\u7889 t ho\u7843 ng tin v\u7873  b\u7919 a ti\u7879 c, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n nguy\u7879 n v\u7885 ng c\'f9ng ng\u7911  trong quan t\'e0i c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7915 ng s\u7907 ." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi vu\u7889 t ve \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng cong n\u417 i eo c\u7853 u, tr\u7845 n an, "Ch\'fang ta ch\u7881  c\u7847 n l\u7897  m\u7863 t m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, sau \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  quay v\u7873  quan t\'e0i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i. Ta bi\u7871 t ng\'e0y mai em ph\u7843 i v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m em qu\'e1 m\u7879 t nh\u7885 c \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
