\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7841 t tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0o r\uc0\u7891 i m\'e0 h\u7855 n v\u7851 n c\'f2n r\'f9 quy\u7871 n m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7849 y vai h\u7855 n: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \u273 \u432 a qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a t\'f4i cho t\'f4i \u273 i, h\'f4m qua kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\u7841 i b\u7883  ng\'e0i n\'e9m \u7903  \u273 \'e2u r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 i xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7845 y ra t\u7915  trong t\u7911  m\u7897 t b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \u432 a cho c\u7853 u: "L\u7877  ph\u7909 c m\u7899 i may xong, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean em th\u7917  xem c\'f3 v\u7915 a kh\'f4ng. B\'e2y gi\u7901  th\u7901 i gian h\u417 i g\u7845 p, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng v\u7915 a th\'ec ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  b\'e0 Alberta s\u7917 a qua, l\u7847 n sau \u273 \u7893 i m\u7897 t b\u7897  nh\u7887  h\u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 May m\'e0 qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u xem ra c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t ch\u7911 ng t\u7897 c r\u7845 t theo k\u7883 p th\u7901 i \u273 \u7841 i, l\u7877  ph\u7909 c c\u361 ng l\'e0 d\'e1ng \'e2u ph\u7909 c hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7841 i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i phong c\'e1ch th\u7901 i Trung C\u7893  m\'e0 n\u7871 u th\u7901 i nay nh\'ecn th\'ec s\u7869  th\u7845 y r\u7845 t k\u7923  qu\'e1i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7863 c xong \u273 \u7913 ng tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7917 a qu\u7923  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u ch\u7881 nh \u7889 ng qu\u7847 n cho c\u7853 u, l\u7841 i \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7881 nh \u7889 ng tay \'e1o v\'e0 c\u7893  \'e1o, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng m\u7899 i h\'edp m\u7855 t \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 c\u7853 u t\u7915  tr\'ean xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i c\u7853 u m\u7897 t l\u432 \u7907 t: "C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , v\u7873  sau c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7921 a theo m\u7851 u n\'e0y c\u7905  nh\u7887  h\u417 n \u273 \u7875  may."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u r\u7845 t nhanh c\u361 ng l\u7845 y \u273 \u7891  ra thay, m\u7863 c \'e1o s\u417 mi \u273 \'f3ng c\'fac \'e1o xong l\u7841 i c\u7889  \'fd ch\'eca tay \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, coi nh\u432  chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean m\'e0 y\'eau c\u7847 u: "A Di\'ean, gi\'fap ta \u273 \'f3ng c\'fac."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m, t\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 m\'e0 c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u s\u7917 a \u7889 ng tay \'e1o cho h\u7855 n, \u273 \'f3ng c\'fac xong li\u7873 n n\u7917 a qu\u7923  s\u7917 a \u7889 ng qu\u7847 n cho h\u7855 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng v\u7915 a l\'e0m, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ng\u7891 i th\u7859 ng l\'ean s\u7917 a l\u7841 i c\u7893  \'e1o cho h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m h\u7855 n kh\u7869  h\u7841  m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i \u273 \'fang l\'fac nh\'ecn nhau. Qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean, v\u7873  sau nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u do em ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? Ta c\u361 ng s\u7869  ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch cho em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n m\'edm m\'f4i kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 i\u7873 u g\'ec, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t tho\'e1ng \u273 \u7887 . Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c li\u7873 n th\u7915 a c\u417  c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, h\'f4n l\'ean tr\'e1n c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'e1m gi\uc0\u7901  t\u7889 i, nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'e1ch m\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 qu\u7847 n \'e1o l\'e0 l\u432 \u7907 t t\u7899 i l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7919 a ti\u7879 c n\'e0y v\u7889 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \u417 n thu\u7847 n l\'e0 v\'ec hoan ngh\'eanh Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\'e0 t\u7893  ch\u7913 c, nh\u432 ng m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c qu\u7843 n gia ti\'ean sinh \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  v\u7899 i Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , chi b\u7857 ng ho\'e0n th\'e0nh nghi th\u7913 c \u273 \'ednh h\'f4n ngay t\u7841 i b\u7919 a ti\u7879 c. Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd \'97\'97 d\'f9 sao nh\u7851 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 trao t\u7915  l\'e2u r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c kh\'e1ch m\u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chu\u7849 n b\u7883  m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i, \u273 \'e1m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c v\u7915 a th\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7913 c m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i v\u7915 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n c\'f9ng \u273 \u7907 i ch\u7911  nh\'e2n xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n\'97 Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer lu\'f4n r\u7845 t \'edt khi xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, th\u7847 n b\'ed c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i tr\u7913  danh \'97\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean mu\u7889 n t\u7893  ch\u7913 c ti\u7879 c trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7911  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean, m\'e0 tin t\u7913 c c\'f2n n\u7863 ng \u273 \'f4 h\u417 n l\'e0, Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  mu\u7889 n \u273 \'ednh h\'f4n v\u7899 i m\u7897 t con ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tin, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i th\u7901 i gian v\'e0 nh\'e2n v\u7853 t ch\'ednh b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, h\u7885  g\u7847 n nh\u432  cho r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 tr\'f2 \u273 \'f9a ng\'e0y C\'e1 th\'e1ng T\u432  nh\u7841 t nh\u7869 o. Nh\u432 ng Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u273 \'f9a, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ai d\'e1m n\'f3i h\u7855 n \u273 ang \u273 \'f9a, cho n\'ean \u273 \'e2y ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 th\u7853 t. Nh\u432 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec to t\'e1t, tuy r\u7857 ng hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\'f4 d\'e2u v\u7851 n c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n h\'f4n l\u7877  \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  s\u417  \u7911 ng cho ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3, chuy\u7875 n h\'f3a th\'e0nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u. N\u259 ng l\u7921 c m\u7841 nh y\u7871 u c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u417  \u7911 ng b\u7883  \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7903 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c s\u417  \u7911 ng cho k\u7867  \u273 \'f3, v\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean v\u7883  V\u432 \u417 ng Phi ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n s\u417  \u7911 ng c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer s\u7869  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c r\u7845 t m\u7841 nh..\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'ean l\'e0 \uc0\u273 \'e1m Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u hi\u7871 u k\u7923 , m\u7897 t nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, c\'f3 d\'f2ng m\'e1u ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o c\u7905  n\'e0o, l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Emmer trong truy\u7873 n thuy\u7871 t c\u7911 a gi\u7899 i Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c th\u7847 n h\u7891 n \u273 i\'ean \u273 \u7843 o nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7853 m ch\'ed mu\u7889 n k\u7871 t h\'f4n v\u7899 i h\u7855 n\'97\'97 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u r\u7845 t \'edt khi c\u7917  h\'e0nh h\'f4n l\u7877 , b\u7903 i t\'ecnh y\'eau v\u7889 n m\'eanh mang b\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 s\u7869  \u273 \u7893 i l\'f2ng, c\'e2n nh\u259 \u769 c \u273 \u7871 n sinh m\u7879 nh d\'e0i \u273 \u7857 ng \u273 \u7861 ng c\u7911 a Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c, kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 th\u7875  cam \u273 oan m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7897 t l\'f2ng \u273 \u7871 n cu\u7889 i, c\'f9ng m\u7897 t Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'e1c b\'ean nhau d\'e0i l\'e2u. B\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  k\u7871 t th\'e0nh quan h\u7879  b\u7841 n \u273 \u7901 i ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i, nh\u432 ng r\u7845 t hi\u7871 m khi k\u7871 t h\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac qu\uc0\u7843 n gia ti\'ean sinh t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7911  nh\'e2n l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i th\'ec ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 ang \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p x\'e0o l\u432 \u7905 i b\'f2, m\'e0 V\u432 \u417 ng phi \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh mong ng\'f3ng d\'f5i theo h\u7855 n: "Ch\u432 a \u273 \u7911 , th\'eam n\u7919 a \u273 i. Ngh\'eanh Chi, cho th\'eam t\u7887 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7893 i s\u7855 c m\'e0 l\u7841 i b\u7887  th\'eam m\u7845 y t\'e9p t\u7887 i v\'e0o ch\u7843 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng c\u7841 nh ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p, kh\u7869  g\'f5 c\u7917 a: "Xin l\u7895 i, \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , th\u7913  cho ta qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y. C\'e1c kh\'e1ch m\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n, ng\'e0i n\'ean mang Tr\'ec ti\'ean sinh quay v\u7873  thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, A Di\'ean mu\u7889 n \u259 n l\u432 \u7905 i b\'f2, ch\u7901  h\u7855 n \u259 n xong r\u7891 i t\'ednh ti\u7871 p." Qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m n\'f3i, "Ph\u7847 n m\u7903  \u273 \u7847 u c\'e1c ng\u432 \u417 i ch\u7911  tr\'ec \u273 i, ta v\'e0 A Di\'ean l\u7897  m\u7863 t m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u259 n no s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 so \u273 o v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i d\u7877  g\u7841 t, c\u361 ng d\u7877  d\u7909 . Cho n\'ean c\'e0ng l\'fac mu\u7889 n l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n x\u7845 u h\u7855 n s\u7869  c\'e0ng s\u7899 m h\u7919 u c\u7847 u t\u7845 t \u7913 ng m\'e0 l\'e0m \u273 \u7891  \u259 n ngon, d\u7895  ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau th\u7853 t vui v\u7867 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Grey g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i thi l\u7877  xong l\u7863 ng y\'ean kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng r\u7901 i \u273 i. Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng t\u7855 t b\u7871 p, m\'fac l\u432 \u7905 i b\'f2 ra \u273 \u297 a \u273 \u7863 t xu\u7889 ng khay, ti\u7879 n tay kh\u7855 c m\u7897 t c\u7911  c\u7843 i tr\u7855 ng, l\u7845 y th\'eam b\'f4ng c\u7843 i xanh \u273 \'e3 lu\u7897 c b\u432 ng l\'ean b\'e0n, \u273 \u7863 t t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau. C\u7847 m chai r\u432 \u7907 u tr\'ean b\'e0n r\'f3t cho hai ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u258 n nhi\u7873 u rau m\u7897 t ch\'fat. U\u7889 ng m\u7897 t \'edt r\u432 \u7907 u, t\u7889 t cho s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e c\u7911 a em." H\u7855 n \'f4n h\'f2a n\'f3i, "Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i g\u7845 p, m\u7897 t ng\'e0y m\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u kia b\'e2y gi\u7901  m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean bi\u7871 t t\u7917 u l\u432 \u7907 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'e9m c\u7905  n\'e0o, d\'f9 l\'e0 r\u432 \u7907 u tr\'e1i c\'e2y n\u7891 ng \u273 \u7897  kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng bao nhi\'eau ch\u7881  u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ch\'e9n c\u361 ng h\'f4n m\'ea. Nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 k\u7871 t qu\u7843  m\'e0 h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  t\u7889 i Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7927  r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 mang theo nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i trong l\u7901 i \u273 \u7891 n xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\'e1c kh\'e1ch m\u7901 i \'97\'97 h\u7855 n ch\u7881  \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  h\'e0nh lang l\u7847 u hai, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\'e0o h\u7887 i v\u7899 i c\'e1c kh\'e1ch trong \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u, kh\'f4ng \u273 i t\u7899 i ch\u7895  c\'e1c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c. Nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\u7873 m nh\u361 n d\u7921 a v\'e0o h\u7855 n, hai m\'e1 \u273 \u7887  \u7917 ng, b\u7897  d\'e1ng tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn r\u7845 t nghe l\u7901 i r\u7845 t \u7927  l\u7841 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ni\u7871 t tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean, cho m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7845 y nh\u7851 n tr\'ean tay em \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u259 n l\u432 \u7905 i b\'f2 b\u7919 a khuya Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7909  d\u7895  u\u7889 ng hai ch\'e9n r\u432 \u7907 u l\u7899 n, \u273 \u7847 u \'f3c s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  n\'ean tr\'ec \u273 \u7897 n, ngay c\u7843  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 h\u7855 n gi\'fap c\u7853 u thay.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n b\'ean tai, v\'f4 th\u7913 c m\'e0 ng\u7917 a m\u7863 t l\'ean n\u7903  m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i th\u7853 t l\u7899 n v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, hai m\'e1 l\'fam \u273 \u7873 u hi\u7879 n ra. C\u7853 u ng\'e2y ng\u7889 c ch\u7889 c l\'e1t m\u7899 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7855 n \u273 ang n\'f3i g\'ec, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c quay \u273 \u7847 u v\u7873  \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u417  tay tr\'e1i l\'ean, n\'e9t c\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng gi\u7843 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t qu\u7843  th\u7921 c b\u7883  c\u7853 u c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n hoa m\u7855 t, tim l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7853 p m\u7841 nh, ho\u7843 ng th\u7847 n m\u7845 t m\u7845 y gi\'e2y li\u7873 n v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \'f4m eo c\u7853 u, ni\u7871 t th\u7883 t m\u7873 m eo tr\'e1i c\u7853 u th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: " A Di\'ean ng\u7889 c, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u432 \u7901 i n\u7919 a, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u432 \u7901 i n\u7919 a . \u272 \u7871 n, \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y, quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn ta, nh\'ecn ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i nghi\'eang m\u7863 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh r\u7891 i n\'e9t m\u7863 t m\u7899 i h\'f2a ho\'e3n l\u7841 i, l\u7845 y ra m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p m\'e0u \u273 en l\u7863 ng l\u7869  nh\'e9t v\'e0o tay \'e1i nh\'e2n, trong mi\u7879 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c d\u7909  d\u7895 : "Ngoan, m\u7903  h\u7897 p ra, l\u7845 y nh\u7851 n b\'ean trong \u273 eo cho ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 nh\u7851 n \u273 \'ednh h\'f4n, ta \u273 \'e3 cho ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i l\'e0m m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c kh\'e1c, l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i v\u7899 i chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n tr\u432 \u7899 c kia ta \u273 \u432 a em, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 b\u7841 c. D\'e1ng nh\u7851 n c\u432 \u7899 i t\'f9y em ch\u7885 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i, v\u432 \u417 n tay tr\'e1i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, c\u7889  \'fd t\'e1ch hai b\'ean ng\'f3n \'e1p \'fat \u273 \u7875  ti\u7879 n cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 eo nh\u7851 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tu\uc0\u7847 n t\u7921  l\'e0m theo l\u7901 i h\u7855 n, \u273 eo xong l\u7841 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, nh\u432  \u273 ang ch\u7901  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c khen.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, d\'f9ng r\u259 ng nanh \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o c\u7893  c\u7853 u \'97\'97 trao \u273 \u7893 i huy\u234 \u769 t di\u803 ch v\u7889 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng nghi th\u7913 c \u273 \'ednh h\'f4n, nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n c\u361 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a. Ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y, t\u7915  khi vui v\u7867  \u259 n xong b\u7919 a khuya, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u m\'ea ho\u7863 c h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\'f9ng n\u7893  ti\u7871 ng ch\'fac m\u7915 ng v\'e0 \'e2m thanh \u7911 ng h\u7897 , huy\'ean n\'e1o m\'e0 vui m\u7915 ng. Ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c c\u361 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng c\u7843 m x\'fac n\'e0y l\'e2y lan, m\u7873 m m\u7841 i m\'e0 \'f4m c\u7893  h\u7855 n, vui v\u7867  nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\'f4i r\u7845 t th\'edch ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7845 y Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c n\'e2ng m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, l\'fac \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n \'e1nh m\u7855 t h\u7855 n l\u7841 i x\u7845 u h\u7893  m\'e0 c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng r\u7841 ng r\u7905 . M\u7895 i l\u7847 n ch\u7845 m d\u7913 t h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bu\'f4ng ra l\u7841 i h\'f4n l\'ean kh\'f3e m\'f4i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\u7843  th\u7921 c h\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ngay l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \'f4m nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i v\'e0o trong quan t\'e0i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh gi\u7845 u k\u7929 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng nghi th\u7913 c v\u7851 n ch\u432 a k\u7871 t th\'fac. X\'e9t th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 con ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, d\u7921 a theo nghi th\u7913 c, b\u432 \u7899 c trao \u273 \u7893 i m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\'e0 h\u7855 n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tr\u7887  tay tr\'e1i, cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\'fat mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Y\uc0\u7871 t h\u7847 u h\u7855 n gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda \'e1i nh\'e2n. A Di\'ean hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i say th\'e0nh c\'e1i d\u7841 ng n\'e0y, tho\'e1ng ngh\u297  qua \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nghi th\u7913 c \u273 \'f3 s\u7869  l\'e0 tra t\u7845 n ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o c\u7905  n\'e0o. Qu\u7843  th\u7921 c l\'e0 th\u7917  th\'e1ch \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n ph\u7843 i l\'e0 t\u7889 c chi\u7871 n t\u7889 c th\u7855 ng th\'f4i. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p d\'f9ng m\'f3ng tay ng\'f3n c\'e1i c\u7855 t ng\'f3n tr\u7887 , \u273 \u432 a ng\'f3n tr\u7887  nhu\u7897 m m\'e1u \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean m\'f4i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng d\u7909  d\u7895 : "Ngoan, A Di\'ean, gi\'fap ta li\u7871 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i, li\u7871 m xong ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  quay v\u7873  ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i \u273 i ng\u7911  r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi u\uc0\u7889 ng say qu\u7843  nhi\'ean d\u7877  b\u7883  l\u7915 a, nghe v\u7853 y li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921 , g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i ng\u7853 m ng\'f3n tay ch\u7843 y m\'e1u c\u7911 a h\u7855 n v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng. H\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i quen thu\u7897 c. C\u7853 u c\u7889  \'fd c\u7849 n th\u7853 n d\'f9ng \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m li\u7871 m \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t th\'e2m tr\u7847 m c\u7911 a qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n d\u7915 ng \u7903  c\u7853 u. C\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c li\u7873 n ng\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, l\u7897  ra n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i vui v\u7867 , tin c\u7853 y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ch\'fat \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi u\uc0\u7889 ng say c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 r\u7845 t th\'edch c\u432 \u7901 i, l\'fac \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fat keo ki\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n th\'e0nh xong. H\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7901  n\u7893 i n\u7919 a r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e2n V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c nghi\'eam m\u7863 t li\u7871 c qu\u7843 n gia c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, sau khi nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u tr\u7843  l\u7901 i kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh li\u7873 n nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda c\'e1c kh\'e1ch m\u7901 i trong \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\'e0o, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7871  \'e1i nh\'e2n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, ti\u7871 ng hoan h\'f4 c\'f9ng ti\u7871 ng ch\'fac m\u7915 ng trong \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh \u273 \u7873 u n\'e9m h\u7871 t ph\'eda sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n tin m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i Grey s\u7869  ti\u7871 p \u273 \'e3i t\u7889 t nh\u7919 ng v\u7883  kh\'e1ch kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\'e3i cho \uc0\u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac b\u7883  \'f4m v\'e0o quan t\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en trong h\u7847 m ng\u7847 m m\u7899 i h\u417 i t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c th\u7843  tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, ng\u7917 a \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\u7841 i sao l\u7841 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i quay v\u7873  \u273 i ng\u7911  m\'e0. Ng\'e0i g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, ng\'e0i l\u7841 i g\u7841 t t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi bi\u7871 t r\'f5 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i ng\u7889 c, t\u432  duy c\u361 ng th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n m\'e0 \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7895  d\'e0nh: "A Di\'ean, ta kh\'f4ng l\u7915 a em. L\'fac s\'e1ng em \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng h\'f4m nay ch\'fang ta ng\u7911  trong quan t\'e0i m\'e0, em qu\'ean r\u7891 i sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y th\u7853 t, tuy r\u7857 ng ch\'ednh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u t\u7841 i sao m\'ecnh l\u7841 i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng. \'c0..., ch\u7855 c c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n l\'e0m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi vui, n\u7871 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'edch th\'ec c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  b\u7909 ng chuy\u7879 n c\'f9ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ng\u7911  trong quan t\'e0i. C\u7853 u nghi\'eam t\'fac g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "V\u7853 y h\'f4m nay ch\'fang ta ng\u7911  trong quan t\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n m\u7903  n\u7855 p quan t\'e0i, \u273 \u7849 y ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau v\'e0o trong, sau \u273 \'f3 b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng n\u7857 m v\'e0o. Trong h\u7847 m ng\u7847 m t\u7889 i m\u7901 , th\'e2n \u7843 nh hai ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n to\'e0n b\u7897  chui v\'e0o trong quan t\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en \'e2m u. M\u7897 t b\'e0n tay thon d\'e0i t\'e1i nh\u7907 t t\u7915  trong quan t\'e0i du\u7895 i ngo\'e0i, chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n m\'e0u b\u7841 c tr\'ean ng\'f3n \'e1p \'fat tay tr\'e1i d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n ph\u7843 n x\u7841  tia s\'e1ng y\u7871 u \u7899 t, b\'e0n tay ch\u7853 m r\'e3i k\'e9o n\u7855 p quan t\'e0i l\u7841 i, ch\u7881  ch\u7915 a m\u7897 t khe h\u7903  \u273 \u7875  kh\'f4ng kh\'ed l\u432 u th\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong quan t\'e0i m\'e0u \uc0\u273 en b\u7853 t ra th\u7903  d\'e0i nhu h\'f2a c\u7911 a Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c: "... B\u7843 o b\u7889 i, ta c\u361 ng y\'eau em..."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 t l\'e2u sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i d\u7847 n t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'ecnh v\'e0 qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 ang \'f4m ch\u7863 t nhau, b\u7889 n ph\'eda r\u7845 t t\u7889 i, kh\'f4ng gian nh\u7887  h\u7865 p m\'e0 b\'edt k\'edn \'97\'97 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 l\u7841 i th\u7915 a c\u417  l\u7915 a m\'ecnh v\'e0o quan t\'e0i r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'dd th\uc0\u7913 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u d\u7847 n kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c, k\'ed \u7913 c l\'fac say r\u432 \u7907 u v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u361 ng \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i tr\u7903  v\u7873 . C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng k\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 c\u7855 n m\u7841 nh m\u7897 t c\'e1i l\'ean c\u7893  qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\'ean c\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u t\'e2m t\'ecnh r\u7845 t t\u7889 t m\'e0 an \u7911 i c\u7853 u: "Ngoan, t\u7881 nh r\u7891 i? \u272 \u7847 u c\'f3 \u273 au kh\'f4ng? Mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Trong b\'f3ng t\uc0\u7889 i m\u7897 t b\'ecnh gi\u7919  nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7903  n\u7855 p u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m, \u273 \u7897  \u7845 m v\u7915 a \u273 \u7911 , h\u417 i ng\u7885 t, l\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7853 t ong.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i v\u7915 a mu\u7889 n n\'f3i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c qu\'ean b\'e9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau m\uc0\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u c\u7853 u l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, ng\'e0i mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 n t\'f4i th\'e0nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t k\u7875  th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 n\'f3i, trao nh\u7851 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t nhi\u7873 u qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u nh\u432  v\u7853 y ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng m\u7897 t nghi th\u7913 c b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o l\u7915 a m\'ecnh d\u7889 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, gi\u7843  v\u7901  b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean ho\u7863 c kh\'f4ng \u273 o\'e1n ra h\'e0m ngh\u297 a trong \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'f4n l\'ean v\'e0nh tai c\u7853 u: "S\u7869  kh\'f4ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang nghi ho\u7863 c b\u7845 t an v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c: "S\u417  \u7911 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c g\'ec t\u7921  tay gi\u7871 t ch\u7871 t em, ta s\u7869  kh\'f4ng h\u7841  th\u7911 , l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng n\u7905 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngay sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i: "Hu\u7889 ng chi em tham \u259 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, bi\u7871 n em th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7883  gi\'e1c, ta sao c\'f3 th\u7875  cam l\'f2ng."\cb1 \
