\f9 \cf4 Ch\uc0\u432 \u417 ng 92: Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\uc0\u432 a h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi bay v\u7873  Sophus.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a c\u7853 u l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh c\u7911 a th\u7871  gi\u7899 i h\u7855 c \'e1m m\'e0 lo\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  hay bi\u7871 t, m\'e1y bay thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i v\u432 \u7907 t qua l\'e3nh th\u7893  m\u7897 t n\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng b\u7883  b\u7845 t k\u7923  tr\u7903  ng\u7841 i n\'e0o. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n visa c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\u7851 n \u273 \u7875  \u7903  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7883  b\u7855 t \u273 \u7871 n l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i visa c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3, b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7913  th\u7871  m\'e0 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh \u273 \u7891  \u259 n nh\u7853 p l\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean thi t\uc0\u7893 ng c\u7897 ng ba m\'f4n, chia \u273 \u7873 u trong th\u7901 i gian thi, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  ng\'e0y m\'f9ng 9 th\'e1ng 6 \u273 \u7871 n ng\'e0y 20 th\'e1ng 6. Hai m\'f4n sau \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean v\u7851 n k\u7883 p \'f4n, c\'f2n m\'f4n thi ng\'e0y m\'f9ng 9 th\'ec \u273 \'e3 h\u417 i g\u7845 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7921  bi\u7871 t \u273 u\u7889 i l\'fd, kh\'f4ng n\'ean d\'f9 bi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\'f3 vi\u7879 c m\'e0 v\u7851 n nh\u7889 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng trong quan t\'e0i l\'e0m x\u7857 ng l\'e0m b\u7853 y, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 a ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau m\'e1y bay ph\u7843 i bay r\u7891 i m\u7899 i th\u7843  ra. H\u7855 n nh\u7899  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  r\u7899 t m\'f4n, c\u7889  \'fd ng\u7847 m d\u7863 n d\'f2 Grey, b\u7843 o \'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  \u273 \'e1nh tr\u432 \u7907 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng h\uc0\u7873  bi\u7871 t vi\u7879 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m, \u273 \'eam h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 sau khi \u273 \u7871 n Sophus, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n c\u7853 u c\'f9ng tr\u7903  v\u7873 , n\'f3i l\'e0 s\'e1ng mai s\u7869  d\u7853 y chu\u7849 n b\u7883  b\u7919 a s\'e1ng cho c\u7853 u r\u7891 i t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u \u273 i thi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe xong v\'f4 c\'f9ng \uc0\u273 \u7897 ng t\'e2m, nh\u432 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7871 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  l\u7841 i c\'f9ng qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y nhau, \u273 \u7871 n s\'e1ng mai l\u7841 i v\u7897 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng v\'e0ng m\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng. Cho n\'ean v\u7851 n l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t: "Kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u7903  v\u7899 i ng\'e0i t\'f4i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\u297 nh t\'e2m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\u417  tay cam \u273 oan n\'f3i: "Ta tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m phi\u7873 n em, \u273 i c\'f9ng ta \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7869  h\'f4n b\'ean m\'f4i h\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y ng\'e0i ch\u7901  t\'f4i, \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh t\u7853 p trung h\u7885 c, nh\'e2n ti\u7879 n suy ng\u7851 m l\u7841 i, t\'f4i ngh\u297  k\u297  r\u7891 i s\u7869  tr\u7903  v\u7873  t\'ecm ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t c\u7853 u trong tr\u7867 o, th\u7847 n s\u7855 c ch\u259 m ch\'fa. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7901  l\'ean m\'f4i, th\u7887 a hi\u7879 p n\'f3i: "V\u7853 y em ngh\u297  nhanh l\'ean m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 u\u7893 i Grey \u273 i, t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\'e1i xe \u273 \u432 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7873  ph\'f2ng, nh\'ecn theo b\'f3ng c\u7853 u \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u7903  l\u7841 i k\'fd t\'fac l\u7845 y m\'e1y t\'ednh b\u7843 ng ra b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u h\u7885 c. H\u7885 c \u273 \u7871 n ba gi\u7901  s\'e1ng th\'ec ng\u7911  m\u7897 t h\u7891 i, \u273 \u7871 n n\u259 m gi\u7901  t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i l\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7885 c, h\u7885 c \u273 \u7871 n b\u7843 y gi\u7901  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7841 m \u7893 n, \u273 \'e3 xem to\'e0n b\u7897  ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh h\u7885 c m\u7897 t l\u432 \u7907 t, c\'e1c m\u7851 u b\'e0i n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 xem qua, v\'ec v\u7853 y b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ng\u7911 , ng\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n t\'e1m r\u432 \u7905 i d\u7853 y \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ch\'edn r\u432 \u7905 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u thi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng th\uc0\u7875  kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh h\u7885 c \u7903  \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau, cu\u7897 c thi n\'e0y kh\'f4ng y\'eau c\u7847 u t\'ednh ra k\u7871 t qu\u7843  cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n l\'e0m b\'e0i theo tr\'ecnh t\u7921  c\'e1c b\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u7841 y l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, h\u417 n n\u7919 a to\'e0n b\u7897  ch\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ecnh h\u7885 c c\u7913  n\u259 m m\u432 \u417 i \u273 i\u7875 m l\'e0 coi nh\u432  \u273 \u7841 t ti\'eau chu\u7849 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi xin ngh\u7881  cho c\u7853 u nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, l\'fd do c\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i Giang \u272 i\u7873 n lu\'f4n l\'e0 "B\u7883  b\u7879 nh, \u273 ang d\u432 \u7905 ng b\u7879 nh \u7903  nh\'e0 b\'e1c" . Thi xong m\'f4n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7853 u h\u7865 n Giang \u272 i\u7873 n g\u7863 p \u7903  qu\'e1n c\'e0 ph\'ea trong tr\u432 \u7901 ng, Giang \u272 i\u7873 n th\u7845 y c\u7853 u c\'e2u \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean l\'e0 h\u7887 i: "Kh\u7887 i r\u7891 i \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\u7887 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n quan t\'e2m n\'f3i: "L\'e0m b\'e0i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 ? C\u7853 u ngh\u7881  nhi\u7873 u th\u7871  m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'e0nh th\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \'e1p: "L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 n\'f3 cao qu\'e1." S\u7899 m bi\u7871 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y h\'f4m qua h\u7885 c hai ti\u7871 ng l\'e0 \u273 \u7911  r\u7891 i, th\u7901 i gian c\'f2n l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  ng\u7911  b\'f9 c\'f2n h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Giang \uc0\u272 i\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7855 ng c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7899  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , visa c\u7911 a c\u7853 u h\'ecnh nh\u432  s\u7855 p h\u7871 t h\u7841 n r\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? \u272 \u7883 nh khi n\'e0o th\'ec v\u7873  n\u432 \u7899 c?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Thi xong t\'f4i s\uc0\u7869  v\u7873  ngay." Tr\'ec Di\'ean khu\u7845 y c\u7889 c c\'e0 ph\'ea, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Giang \u272 i\u7873 n, "\u272 \u7907 i c\u7853 u v\u7873  n\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i b\u7885 n m\'ecnh li\'ean l\u7841 c l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
