\cb3 Sau khi k\'ec thi k\uc0\u7871 t th\'fac, tr\u432 \u7899 c khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean tra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u7871 t qu\u7843  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh th\'ec Grey \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m l\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u7871 t qu\u7843  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, t\u7901  b\'e1o \u273 i\u7875 m c\u361 ng tr\'ecnh l\'ean cho Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng: "\u272 i\u7879 n h\u7841 , b\'e0i thi c\u7911 a V\u432 \u417 ng Phi r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ta nh\'fang tay v\'e0o."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "C\'e1c m\'f4n A Di\'ean \u273 \u7873 u qua h\u7871 t \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'fang v\u7853 y." Grey nh\'ecn qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  n\'f3i, "C\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "A Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7863 t v\'e9 m\'e1y bay v\u7873  n\u432 \u7899 c? Ng\u432 \u417 i mu\u7889 n b\'e1o ta vi\u7879 c n\'e0y?" N\'e9t m\u7863 t Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng v\u7851 n r\u7845 t b\'ecnh t\u297 nh nh\u432  c\u361 , h\u7855 n vu\u7889 t ve chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n tr\'ean ng\'f3n \'e1p \'fat tay tr\'e1i, l\'e0 chi\u7871 c nh\u7851 n \u273 \'ednh h\'f4n m\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 t\u7921  tay \u273 eo cho h\u7855 n, tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  h\u7855 n c\u361 ng ch\u432 a ch\'ednh th\u7913 c n\'f3i cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\u7871 t r\u7857 ng ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'ednh h\'f4n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "Ta bi\uc0\u7871 t r\u7891 i, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  m\'e1y bay \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7891 i tr\'ean gh\u7871  r\u7897 ng, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e1y bay c\u7845 t c\'e1nh, bay l\'ean cao, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u n\u7919 a c\u7853 u s\u7869  ho\'e0n to\'e0n r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i nam b\'e1n c\u7847 u, tr\u7903  v\u7873  qu\'ea h\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n ch\u7841 y, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7915 a g\u7841 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  ch\u7881  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m g\u7863 p Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7891 i \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e2m, tr\u7847 m lu\'e2n \u273 \u7873 u qu\'e1 nhanh, kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, kh\'f4ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t y\'eau c\u7847 u c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, ch\u7881  h\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 em b\u7843 n th\'e2n t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u cho h\u7855 n, ng\u7911  quan t\'e0i g\'ec g\'ec \u273 \'f3 k\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  so \u273 o, n\u7871 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'edch, c\u7853 u s\u7861 n l\'f2ng m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u ng\u7911  trong quan t\'e0i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n. Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\'edch ai, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh y\'eau s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ki\u7875 u nh\u432  h\u7855 n, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng hay kh\'f4ng, c\u7853 u ngh\u297  sau khi hi\u7875 u r\'f5 r\'e0ng t\'e2m \'fd c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n r\u7891 i s\u7869  cho h\u7855 n c\'e2u tr\u7843  l\u7901 i ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\u7913  thu\u7853 n theo t\'e2m \'fd, d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng v\'e0 b\u7843 n n\u259 ng m\'e0 c\'f9ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y nhau nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ch\'ednh m\'ecnh v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 v\'f4 tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\'ednh to\'e1n k\u7929  c\'e0ng, th\u7915 a d\u7883 p ngh\u7881  h\'e8 n\u7897 p CV v\'e0o m\u7897 t v\'e0i c\'f4ng ty \u273 \u7875  \u273 i th\u7921 c t\u7853 p, trong \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 m\u7897 t n\u417 i g\u7885 i c\u7853 u ng\'e0y mai \u273 i ph\u7887 ng v\u7845 n. Hai th\'e1ng l\u432 \u417 ng th\u7921 c t\u7853 p h\'e8 kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7911  cho c\u7853 u tr\u7843  ti\u7873 n v\'e9 kh\u7913  h\u7891 i \u273 i ch\'e2u \'c2u, gia h\u7841 n visa v\'e0 thanh to\'e1n c\'e1c chi ph\'ed li\'ean quan kh\'e1c. C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh, xin ti\u7873 n ra n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i \u273 i g\u7863 p ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh th\u7853 t s\u7921  r\u7845 t ng\u7841 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng v\u7899 i ba m\u7865 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 ang t\'ednh to\'e1n trong b\u7909 ng, nh\'e2n vi\'ean ph\u7909 c v\u7909  \u273 i t\u7899 i nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i th\u259 m c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean thu\uc0\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i u\u7889 ng tr\'e0, nh\'e2n vi\'ean ph\u7909 c v\u7909  l\u7841 i n\'f3i t\'ean m\u7897 t lo\u7841 t c\'e1c lo\u7841 i tr\'e0, h\u7887 i c\u7853 u u\u7889 ng tr\'e0 g\'ec. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7885 n tr\'e0 Long T\u7881 nh. Tr\'e0 \u7845 m v\u7915 a tay, l\'e0 d\'f9ng n\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3ng ng\'e2m t\'fai tr\'e0, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t khay qu\u7843  kh\'f4.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i c\u7843 m \u417 n. V\'e9 m\'e1y bay c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 do nh\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c chi tr\u7843  \u273 \u7863 t thay, ti\'eau chu\u7849 n th\u7889 ng nh\u7845 t l\'e0 khoang ph\u7893  th\'f4ng h\'e3ng h\'e0ng kh\'f4ng Trung Qu\u7889 c, cho n\'ean c\u7853 u bay \u273 i bay v\u7873  \u273 \u7873 u ng\u7891 i Air China. K\u7871 t qu\u7843  tr\u432 \u7899 c h\'f4m \u273 \u259 ng k\'fd m\u7897 t ng\'e0y nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin h\'e3ng bay g\u7917 i \u273 \u7871 n, n\'f3i l\'e0 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c quy\u7873 n th\u259 ng khoang, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ti\u7871 n h\'e0nh \u273 \u259 ng k\'fd b\'e8n ch\u7885 n th\u7859 ng khoang h\u7841 ng nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao c\uc0\u361 ng l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n t\u7889 t, vi\u7879 c th\u259 ng khoang mi\u7877 n ph\'ed t\u7841 m th\u7901 i n\'e0y c\u361 ng l\'fac c\'f3 ph\'e1t sinh, kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 qu\'e1 k\u7923  l\u7841 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t nguy\'ean nh\'e2n m\'ecnh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u259 ng khoang, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n r\u7845 t vui v\u7867  ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n. H\'e0nh tr\'ecnh h\u417 n m\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  tho\u7843 i m\'e1i th\'eam ch\'fat n\'e0o th\'ec hay ch\'fat \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac c\u7845 t c\'e1nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\'f3i c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n v\u7873  n\u432 \u7899 c suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i s\u7869  \u273 i t\'ecm h\u7855 n, g\u7917 i xong l\u7841 i c\'f3 ch\'fat kinh s\u7907 , kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7855 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n hay kh\'f4ng, s\u7869  ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng th\u7871  n\'e0o, c\u7853 u d\u7913 t kho\'e1t ho\u7863 c l\'e0 kh\'f4ng l\'e0m, \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m th\'ec cho xong, g\u7885 i th\u7859 ng cho nh\'e0 m\u7841 ng \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  x\'f3a b\u7887  s\u7889  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. C\u7853 u t\u7921  an \u7911 i trong l\'f2ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mu\u7889 n li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i c\u7853 u ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  c\'f3 c\'e1ch, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n \'fd c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, cho c\u7853 u th\u7901 i gian v\'e0 kh\'f4ng gian suy ngh\u297  th\u7853 t k\u7929 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean tuy\u7879 t kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i sau khi xu\u7889 ng m\'e1y bay, c\u7853 u v\u7915 a k\'e9o vali \u273 i ra \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng trong \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh s\'e2n bay ch\u7901  m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong n\uc0\u432 \u7899 c \u273 ang l\'e0 gi\u7919 a h\'e8, Th\'e2n V\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n t\'e2y \u273 en v\u7899 i \'e1o s\u417  mi tr\u7855 ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, \'e1o s\u417 mi x\u7855 n l\'ean c\'e1nh tay, r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 c\'e1ch \u259 n m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i cao g\u7847 y ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh n\u7893 i b\u7853 t, ch\u7881  t\'f9y \'fd \u273 \u7913 ng trong \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng thu h\'fat \'e1nh m\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia ti\'ean sinh bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng hai tay, cung k\'ednh \u273 \u7913 ng ph\'eda sau h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\'e1 to mi\uc0\u7879 ng, s\u7919 ng s\u7901  t\u7841 i ch\u7895 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 i t\u7899 i, t\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n vali trong tay c\u7853 u nh\u432  \u273 i \u273 \'f3n b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, \'e2n c\u7847 n n\'f3i: "C\'f3 m\u7879 t kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao ng\'e0i...l\uc0\u7841 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y? Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, ng\'e0i \u273 \u7885 c tin nh\u7855 n t\'f4i g\u7917 i cho ng\'e0i ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e3 \u273 \u7885 c, sau \u273 \'f3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ngay c\u7843  s\u7889  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i em c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m gi\u7919  l\u7841 i. Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i d\'e1m l\'e0m m\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7883 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n quay \u273 \u7847 u sang nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i: "Ta \u273 \u7885 c r\u7891 i, ta ho\'e0n to\'e0n \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd v\u7899 i em. Cho n\'ean h\'f4m qua ta \u273 \'e3 b\u7843 o Grey \u273 \u7863 t mua nh\'e0 trong n\u432 \u7899 c, em c\u7913  t\u7915  t\u7915  suy ngh\u297 , ta b\u7891 i em."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng t\'f4i ch\u7881  c\u7847 n v\u7915 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ng\'e0i li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t th\'edch ng\'e0i... Ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o b\'ecnh \u7893 n tinh th\u7847 n m\'e0 t\u7853 p trung suy ngh\u297 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi im l\u7863 ng n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t tay c\u7853 u: "V\u7853 y th\'ec c\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c th\'edch, v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n t\u7881 nh t\'e1o n\u7919 a. \u272 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 u ta mu\u7889 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong s\'e2n bay \uc0\u7891 n \'e0o, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i t\u7915  ch\'e2u \'dac v\u7855 ng v\u7867  tr\u7903  v\u7873  r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng quen, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7849 y \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y. C\u7853 u k\'e9o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ng\'e0i l\'e1i xe t\u7899 i hay sao? Quay v\u7873  xe r\u7891 i n\'f3i ti\u7871 p."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\'f3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  m\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n, h\u7855 n giao h\u7871 t h\'e0nh l\'fd c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean cho Grey, b\u7843 o Grey l\'e1i xe mang v\u7873 , sau \u273 \'f3 d\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'ean m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c xe kh\'e1c. V\u7915 a l\'ean xe h\u7855 n li\u7873 n k\'e9o tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e8 l\'ean ng\u7921 c tr\'e1i m\'ecnh, ch\'e2n th\'e0nh n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean, ta v\'e0 em gi\u7889 ng nhau. Ta c\'f2n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y em h\u7841  ch\'fa ta, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng l\'e0m sao ta v\u7915 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y em li\u7873 n nh\u432  b\u7883  m\'ea t\'e2m r\u7891 i, tr\u7915  em ra c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n bu\'f4ng tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \'e1p tr\'e1n m\'ecnh l\'ean tr\'e1n c\u7853 u, c\'f9ng c\u7853 u m\u432 \u7901 i ng\'f3n \u273 an xen: "\u272 \u7915 ng g\u7845 p, ch\'fang ta c\'f9ng nhau ngh\u297 , ngh\u297  c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao. \u272 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 n\u7871 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  ngh\u297  m\'e3i kh\'f4ng ra, v\u7853 y th\'ec kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ngh\u297  n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Theo nh\uc0\u432  l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Tr\'ec Di\'ean qu\u7843  \u273 \'fang l\'e0 ngh\u297  t\u7899 i ngh\u297  lui cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng qu\'ean lu\'f4n ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi t\uc0\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, b\u7903 i v\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'ean c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 xin h\u7885 c nghi\'ean c\u7913 u sinh \u7903  \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c b\'ean ch\'e2u \'c2u, c\u361 ng v\'e0o l\'fac t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p nghi\'ean c\u7913 u sinh th\'ec th\'e0nh h\'f4n v\u7899 i h\u7855 n trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i. \u272 \u7889 i v\u7899 i b\u7841 n b\'e8 th\'e2n quen Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7873 u d\u7889 i l\'e0 trong l\'fac h\u7885 c \u7903  \u273 \'e2y th\'ec quen bi\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u v\'e0 Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841  sau khi n\u7895  l\u7921 c tr\u7843 i qua m\u7885 i kh\'f3 kh\u259 n gian kh\u7893 , cha m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd quan h\u7879  c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Ng\'e0y th\'e0nh h\'f4n, cha m\uc0\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'e9o c\u7853 u qua m\u7897 t b\'ean l\u7863 ng l\u7869  n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean \'e0, b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\u7911 a v\u7907  con th\u7853 t l\'e0 nhi\u7873 u, \u273 \'f4ng ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7921  nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Xem ra th\u7871  l\u7921 c nh\'e0 th\'f4ng gia th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng t\u7847 m th\u432 \u7901 ng, con c\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, sau n\'e0y ph\u7843 i nh\u432 \u7901 ng v\u7907  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ch\'fa \'fd b\u7843 o v\u7879  m\'ecnh ch\u7899  \u273 \u7875  b\u7883  \u7913 c hi\u7871 p."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn nh\'ecn c\uc0\u7843  ph\'f2ng to\'e0n qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u, nghe ba m\u7865  n\'f3i, r\'fat cu\u7897 c minh b\u7841 ch t\u7841 i sao m\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean t\u7921  nhi\'ean s\u7907  h\'e3i r\u7891 i, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 di truy\u7873 n c\u7843 . C\u7853 u an \u7911 i ba m\u7865  n\'f3i: "Ba m\u7865  \u273 \u7873 u th\u7845 y r\u7891 i m\'e0, Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i con t\u7889 t l\u7855 m, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u t\u7921  m\'ecnh n\u7845 u c\u417 m cho con, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u7913 c hi\u7871 p con \u273 \'e2u, y\'ean t\'e2m \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i Tr\'ec ph\u7909  c\'f9ng Tr\'ec m\u7851 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh, Tr\'ec ph\u7909  n\'f3i th\u7847 m v\u7899 i phu nh\'e2n: "Kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao t\'f4i c\u7913  c\'f3 \u7843 o gi\'e1c \u273 \'e3 g\u7843  con trai \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec m\uc0\u7851 u ph\u7909  h\u7885 a: "\u7846 y, t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y v\u7853 y, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i li\u7871 c nhau. Tr\'ec ph\u7909  ph\u7845 t ph\u7845 t tay: "Th\'f4i th\'f4i m\u7863 c k\u7879  n\'f3, nu\'f4i ti\u7875 u t\u7917  th\'fai kia l\u7899 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u361 ng tho\'e1t r\u7891 i, v\u7873  sau c\u7913  \u273 \u7875  v\u7907  n\'f3 qu\u7843 n \u273 i."\cb1 \
