\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi t\uc0\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p \u7903  l\u7841 i \'c2u Ch\'e2u l\'e0m vi\u7879 c. Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i k\u7871 t h\'f4n xong m\u7895 i th\'e1ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7873 u cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean u\u7889 ng m\'e1u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, b\u7903 i v\'ec m\'e1u h\u7855 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n duy tr\'ec b\u7873  ngo\'e0i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i, nh\'ecn t\u7915  v\u7867  ngo\'e0i xem ra n\u259 m th\'e1ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i tr\'ean c\u7853 u qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u d\u7845 u v\u7871 t. Th\u7901 i tr\u7867  c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng qua loa g\u7841 t \u273 i, nh\u432 ng qua b\u7889 n m\u432 \u417 i tu\u7893 i m\'e0 v\u7867  ngo\'e0i m\'e3i m\'e3i d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i th\'ec kh\'f4ng d\u7877  gi\u7843 i th\'edch l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7913 t kho\'e1t \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  c\u7853 u ngh\u7881  h\u432 u, \u7903  trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i b\u7891 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd. D\'f9 b\u7873  ngo\'e0i tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i th\u7871  n\'e0o, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'ean trong \u273 ang d\u7847 n d\u7847 n suy ki\u7879 t, s\u7913 c l\u7921 c c\u7853 u hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i so v\u7899 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m m\u7899 i quen Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 c\'e1ch r\u7845 t xa. C\u7853 u hi\u7875 u r\'f5 nh\'e2n sinh c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 qua h\u417 n n\u7917 a, so v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh y\'eau g\u7847 n nh\u432  v\u297 nh sinh b\u7845 t t\u7917 , th\u7901 i gian c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c l\'e0m b\u7841 n v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u. Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 b\'ean nhau hai m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m, m\'e0 nhi\u7873 u nh\u7845 t l\'e0 th\'eam ba b\u7889 n m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m n\u7919 a, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u7887 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ch\u432 a g\u7863 p m\'ecnh, h\u417 n m\u7897 t ngh\'ecn n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n tr\'f4i qua nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7845 t b\'ecnh th\u7843 n m\'e0 tr\u7843  l\u7901 i nh\'ecn m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i m\u7885 c, ng\u7855 m m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i l\u7863 n, n\u7857 m trong quan t\'e0i ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c, v\'e0i tr\u259 m n\u259 m li\u7873 n qua. T\u7881 nh l\u7841 i th\u7845 y th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec th\'fa v\u7883 , l\u7841 i ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c, l\u7841 i l\'e0 m\u7845 y tr\u259 m n\u259 m n\u7919 a \u273 \'e3 tr\'f4i qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi do d\uc0\u7921  th\u7853 t l\'e2u, h\u7887 i h\u7855 n c\'f3 ngh\u297  t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n sau khi m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y n\u7919 a th\'ec h\u7855 n s\u7869  l\'e0m g\'ec kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, tr\u7847 m ng\'e2m, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 h\u7887 i: "A Di\'ean, em \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i ch\u432 a, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7841 i \u7903  b\'ean ta." T\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \'e1i nh\'e2n tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p sinh kh\'ed v\'e0 s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng, h\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng n\u7905  bi\u7871 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y A Di\'ean ho\'e0n to\'e0n r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i h\u7855 n, \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i h\u7855 n \u273 u\u7893 i kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p t\'ecm kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y, nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean h\u7855 n l\u7841 i c\'e0ng mu\u7889 n d\'f9ng ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c n\'e0y v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n gi\u7919  \'e1i nh\'e2n l\u7841 i, gi\u7919  l\u7841 i ngay b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'f2ng \u273 \u7847 y k\u7923  v\u7885 ng ch\u7901  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, tr\'ean m\u7863 t l\u7897  ra th\u7847 n s\u7855 c \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n m\'e0 m\u7901  m\u7883 t: "Kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n. N\u7871 u nh\u432  em c\'f3 sinh m\u7879 nh d\'e0i l\'e2u, ng\'e0i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n em n\u7919 a th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao? N\u7871 u ng\'e0i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\u7899 i em, kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i em n\u7919 a th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao? Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, em kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'f4ng y\'eau ng\'e0i, n\u7871 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\'e0y ng\'e0i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n em n\u7919 a, em ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh ch\u7901  ng\'e0i... Ch\u7901  ng\'e0i quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn em m\u7897 t l\u7847 n. Em kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n, kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y... R\u7845 t tuy\u7879 t v\u7885 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\u7889 c s\u7913 c l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, trong m\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 y \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a, t\u7921 a nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \'f3. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 au l\'f2ng \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c an \u7911 i, trong mi\u7879 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng l\u7863 p \u273 i l\u7863 p l\u7841 i "L\'e0m sao ta l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n em ch\u7913 " "Ta n\'e0o c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 em " "A Di\'ean \u273 \u7915 ng nghi ng\u7901  ta" "Ngoan, kh\'f4ng sao, ta v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y" ...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y qua th\u7853 t l\'e2u sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i d\u7847 n an t\u297 nh l\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng t\u7915  \u273 \'f3 v\u7873  sau Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\u7855 c l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y. \'cdt nh\u7845 t hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh h\u7855 n, thu\u7897 c v\u7873  h\u7855 n. H\u7855 n s\u7869  lu\'f4n n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t A Di\'ean c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u259 m th\'e1ng l\u7863 ng l\u7869  tr\'f4i, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i b\u7847 u b\u7841 n \u273 \'e3 l\u7841 i qua b\u7889 n m\u432 \u417 i m\'f9a xu\'e2n thu.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m l\u7841 i m\u7897 t m\'f9a xu\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\'ecnh ch\u7881  s\u7907  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ki\'ean tr\'ec \u273 \u7871 n m\'f9a sen n\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m bi\u7871 t sinh m\u7879 nh m\'ecnh s\u7855 p \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\u7847 n cu\u7889 i, c\u7853 u m\u7899 i ph\'e1t gi\'e1c d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng \u273 \u7897 c chi\u7871 m c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau h\'f3a ra l\u7841 i m\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y. Hy v\u7885 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u7903  trong sinh m\u7879 nh d\'e0i \u273 \u7857 ng \u273 \u7861 ng bu\u7891 n ch\'e1n c\'f3 th\u7875  y\'eau m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7861 n l\'f2ng bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u b\u7891 i h\u7855 n, sau \u273 \'f3 qu\'ean m\'ecnh \u273 i, nh\u432  v\u7853 y h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\'f4 qu\u7841 nh n\u7919 a, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  c\u7847 n v\u7915 a ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n kh\u7843  n\u259 ng \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 au l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i. \u272 \'f3 l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n nh\u432 \u7901 ng cho b\u7845 t k\'ec k\u7867  n\'e0o kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng n\u259 m qua \u7903  b\'ean nhau Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n lu\'f4n ch\u7881  h\'fat m\'e1u c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i \u273 i h\'fat m\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
