\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\u7921 a theo chi ti\u7871 t n\'e0y, d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  tr\u7907  gi\'fap c\u7911 a Grey m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u r\'fat ra m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n m\'e1u c\u7845 t gi\u7919  trong l\'e2u \u273 \'e0i, c\u361 ng \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t d\u7863 n d\'f2 qu\u7843 n gia ti\'ean sinh \u273 \u7907 i sau khi c\u7853 u ch\u7871 t m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'f3i cho Th\'e2n v\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u nh\u432  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9ng \'edt m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ch\u7895  m\'e1u c\u7853 u l\u432 u l\u7841 i c\'f3 \u273 \u7911  cho \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng u\u7889 ng v\'e0i n\u259 m kh\'f4ng? \'cdt nh\u7845 t m\u7897 t n\u259 m c\u361 ng \u273 \u7911  ch\u7913 ? C\u7853 u h\u7889 i h\u7853 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y s\u7899 m m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng trong kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \'edt nh\u7845 t c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7911  m\'e1u cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi u\u7889 ng m\u432 \u7901 i n\u259 m r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 ... Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y, \'edt nh\u7845 t m\u432 \u7901 i n\u259 m sau khi em ch\u7871 t, ng\'e0i v\u7851 n s\u7869  nh\u7899  v\u7873  em, v\u7851 n c\'f2n thu\u7897 c v\u7873  em \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e1ng ti\u7871 c hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u th\u7901 i gian, c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p m\u7895 i ng\'e0y m\u7845 t qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u m\'e1u, th\u7853 m ch\'ed ngay c\u7843  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng c\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\u432  t\'f9y \'fd h\'fat m\'e1u nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 li\'ean t\u7909 c b\u7843 y ng\'e0y kh\'f4ng u\u7889 ng m\'e1u c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\uc0\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \'fd th\u7913 c m\u417  h\u7891  m\'e0 ngh\u297 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng suy y\u7871 u, b\'e1c s\u297  \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  c\u7853 u t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t n\u7857 m t\u297 nh d\u432 \u7905 ng tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng. B\'e1c s\u297  kh\'e1m b\u7879 nh cho c\u7853 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, r\u7845 t ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean vi\u7879 c b\u7873  ngo\'e0i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7907 p v\u7899 i suy ki\u7879 t b\'ean trong, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7871 p s\u7907  uy th\u7871  \'f4ng ch\u7911  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7889  g\u7855 ng t\u7915  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, \u273 \u7905  t\u432 \u7901 ng, t\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t \u273 i d\u7885 c theo th\u7873 m \u273 \'e1 ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p v\u7873  ph\'eda th\'f4ng v\u7899 i h\u7847 m \u273 \u7863 t quan t\'e0i. C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m ngh\u297  k\u7929 , \u273 \u7907 i c\u7853 u ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i chi\u7871 m l\u7845 y quan t\'e0i c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u432  v\u7853 y d\'f9 sau n\'e0y qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u c\'f3 y\'eau ai kh\'e1c, v\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o mang ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7871 n quan t\'e0i thu\u7897 c v\u7873  b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\'e0 ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 107 b\uc0\u7853 c thang, c\u7853 u \u7903  trong n\u417 i n\'e0y m\u7845 y ch\u7909 c n\u259 m \u273 \'e3 \u273 i qua v\'f4 s\u7889  l\u7847 n. B\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'e0 m\u7897 t l\u7847 n cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng, c\u7853 u \u273 i tr\u7885 n v\u7865 n m\u7897 t gi\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7883 n l\'ean th\'e0nh quan t\'e0i, kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7889 n \u273 i cho n\u7845 u ch\'e1o cho ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u432 ng ch\'e1o quay v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ta v\u7853 y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7903  \u273 \'e2y. H\u7855 n r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u417 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ch\u7841 y xu\u7889 ng, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u273 ang v\u7883 n hai tay l\'ean th\'e0nh quan t\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en, nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng vang ch\u7853 m r\'e3i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean, m\u7903  \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u \u273 en v\'f4 t\u7897 i nh\'ecn m\'ecnh, h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, \'f4m em v\'e0o. Ng\'e0i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng t\u7863 ng em quan t\'e0i n\'e0y r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e3 bao nhi\'eau tu\u7893 i r\u7891 i m\'e0 c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m n\u361 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng d\u7921  c\u7843 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7873 u g\'ec \u273 \'f3, n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia b\u7871  c\u7853 u l\'ean, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \u7863 t v\'e0o trong quan t\'e0i, d\u7883 u d\'e0ng nh\'ecn hai m\u7855 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: "Ngoan, l\'e3o c\'f4ng \'f4m em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\uc0\u7857 m b\'ean trong, nh\'ecn h\u7855 n n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7897  ra hai m\'e1 l\'fam \u273 \u7891 ng ti\u7873 n th\u7853 t s\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7855 c \'fd nh\u432  con tr\u7867  m\'e0 khoe khoang: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, em c\'f3 th\u7913  \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i cho ng\'e0i \u273 \u7845 y, sau khi ng\'e0i ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y Grey s\u7869  gi\'fap em giao cho ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c c\'fai xu\u7889 ng kh\u7869  h\'f4n tr\'e1n c\u7853 u, \u273 \u432 a tay ra s\u7917 a l\u7841 i t\'f3c mai cho c\u7853 u, thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "Em n\'f3i ch\u7895  m\'e1u kia sao? Ta u\u7889 ng h\u7871 t r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c m\u7903  to hai m\u7855 t, o\'e1n tr\'e1ch m\'e0 nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, n\'e9t m\u7863 t tho\'e1ng kh\u7893  s\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7889 n t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng, \'edt nh\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh y\'eau nh\u7899  th\u432 \u417 ng m\'ecnh th\'eam m\u7897 t n\u259 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u ch\u7881  kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4n h\'f4n m\'f4i c\u7853 u. M\'e1u c\u7911 a A Di\'ean, h\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng n\u7905  \u273 \u7875  d\u432  l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh y\'eau: "A Di\'ean, em v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n c\'f9ng ta v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n b\'ean nhau sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t m\u7879 t m\u7887 i, c\u7853 u t\u7915  t\u7915  nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, thanh \'e2m r\u7845 t nh\u7887 : "Kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n... kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u l\u7855 m... Ch\u7901  ng\'e0i... th\u7853 t s\u7921  r\u7845 t kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong l\'f2ng d\'e2ng l\'ean m\u7897 t n\u7895 i bi ai kh\'f4n t\u7843 . H\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7841 i sao, trong ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c A Di\'ean lu\'f4n cho r\u7857 ng h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n c\u7853 u, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\u7899 i c\u7853 u, m\'e0 c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7897 t m\u7921 c ch\u7901  h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 " Sao ta c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  b\u7855 t em ch\u7901  ta ch\u7913 ..." H\u7855 n th\'ec th\u7847 m, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i \u273 \u432 a c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0o trong quan t\'e0i, \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, m\u7897 t l\u7847 n cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng d\'f9ng m\'f4i mi\'eau t\u7843  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e9t g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t \'e1i nh\'e2n, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\u7845 y ra t\u7915  trong tay \'e1o m\u7897 t con dao b\u7841 c \u273 \'e3 gi\u7845 u s\u7861 n, r\u7845 t nhanh c\u7855 t c\u7893  tay tr\'e1i Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n k\'edch th\'edch, tho\'e1ng c\'e1i l\u7841 i m\u7903  m\u7855 t m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi... Ng\'e0i mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng m\'e1u \u432 ... T\u7841 i sao kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng r\u259 ng..."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e1u t\uc0\u432 \u417 i nh\u7887  tr\'ean l\u432 \u7905 i dao, tr\u432 \u7907 t xu\u7889 ng m\u361 i dao, r\u7891 i to\'e0n b\u7897  th\u7845 m v\'e0o s\u7889 ng l\u432 ng thanh dao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nhu h\'f2a c\u432 \u7901 i an \u7911 i c\u7853 u, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7869  li\u7871 m m\'e1u tr\'ean c\u7893  tay c\u7853 u, nh\'ecn mi\u7879 ng v\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng nhanh ch\'f3ng kh\'e9p l\u7841 i v\u7899 i t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  m\u7855 t th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u tho\'e1ng c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, tay ph\u7843 i l\u7841 i r\u7845 t nhanh gi\u417  dao ph\u7911  k\'edn m\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u273 \'e2m l\'ean tim m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n r\'fat dao n\'e9m sang m\u7897 t b\'ean, m\'e1u Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c tu\'f4n ra, nhu\u7897 m \u273 \u7847 y tay h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, d\'f9ng b\'e0n tay t\'e1i nh\u7907 t d\'ednh \u273 \u7847 y m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i n\'e2ng m\u7863 t \'e1i nh\'e2n, m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, ta v\'e0 em c\'f9ng \u273 i, ta v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n c\'f9ng em."\cb1 \
\cb3 "... Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u, A Di\'ean, \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng ta, \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng ta. N\u7871 u nh\u432  c\'f3 m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, b\'ean ta \u273 \u7871 n v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n... c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'f9ng s\uc0\u7913 c l\u7921 c l\u7899 n nh\u7845 t c\'f2n l\u7841 i \'f4m l\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c \u273 \u7847 y m\u7863 t: "... \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng ng\'e0i, b\u7845 t k\u7875  bao l\'e2u, \u273 \u7873 u b\'ean ng\'e0i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i xong, thanh \'e2m d\u7847 n d\u7847 n nh\u7887  xu\u7889 ng, hai m\u7855 t c\u361 ng ch\u7853 m r\'e3i nh\u7855 m l\u7841 i. M\u7897 t gi\u7885 t n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t t\u7915  kh\'f3e m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 kh\'e9p k\'edn ch\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7871 t t\u7897 c \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c, b\'e0y ra t\u432  th\u7871  ng\u7911  ng\'e0y th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i. M\u7897 t b\'e0n tay t\'e1i nh\u7907 t nhu\u7897 m m\'e1u \u273 \u7887  t\u432 \u417 i v\u432 \u417 n ra t\u7915  trong quan t\'e0i, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i kh\'e9p n\u7855 p quan t\'e0i l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 \'e2y, k\'edn k\u7869 , kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i b\u7845 t k\'ec khe h\u7903  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  ng\'e0y bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh Huy\u7871 t t\u7897 c \u273 \'f3, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t c\'e1ch duy nh\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7871 t ch\u7871 t m\'ecnh, ch\'ednh l\'e0 d\'f9ng dao b\u7841 c d\'ednh m\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n y\'eau \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o tim h\u7855 n. N\u7871 u nh\u432  h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng y\'eau ai, v\u7853 y s\u7869  v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 y\'eau m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, li\u7873 n cam nguy\u7879 n c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 A Di\'ean, em r\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i r\u7891 i, th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ta c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \'fd ngh\u297 a g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Quan t\'e0i m\'e0u \uc0\u273 en v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n phong k\'edn, qu\u7927  h\'fat m\'e1u \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh y\'eau, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
