\cf2 \cb3 Trong h\'e0nh lang t\uc0\u7889 i t\u259 m kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n trong kh\'f4ng gian y\'ean t\u297 nh \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngu\uc0\u7891 n s\'e1ng duy nh\u7845 t l\'e0 t\u7915  di \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i s\u7907 , c\u7853 u b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u h\u7889 i h\u7853 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7911  quan, ch\u432 a chu\u7849 n b\u7883  c\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n th\u7859 ng \u273 \'e2y. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i cho T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m bi\u7871 t, cho d\'f9 n\'f3i th\'ec T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  tin \'97\'97 r\u7857 ng k\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7907  ma, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t ph\u7843 i ki\'ean c\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh s\'e1ng m\'e0n h\'ecnh kh\'f4ng h\uc0\u7873  c\'f3 d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean t\u7855 t, c\u7843  h\'e0nh lang ho\'e0n to\'e0n ch\'ecm v\'e0o b\'f3ng t\u7889 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7845 t di \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t t\u7855 t, ng\u7915 ng ngay t\u7841 i ch\u7895 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 ang \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t b\'e0n tay nh\u7887  s\u7907  h\'e3i k\'e9o v\u7841 t \'e1o c\u7853 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'e9 g\'e1i \u273 ang s\u7907  h\'e3i k\'e9o m\'ecnh, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang s\u7907  th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3. C\'f4 b\'e9 nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng c\u7847 u kh\u7849 n: "Ch\'fa d\u7851 n con ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? \u7902  \u273 \'e2y t\u7889 i qu\'e1, l\u7841 nh qu\'e1, con s\u7907  l\u7855 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nu\uc0\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t, c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng h\u7841  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn b\'e9 g\'e1i \u273 ang k\'e9o m\'ecnh, n\'f3i kh\u7869 : "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u417  b\u7855 p c\u7893  h\u7885 ng \u273 ang c\u259 ng l\'ean. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng th\'ec t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u432 \u417 ng v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c \u273 em b\u7843 y t\'e1m ph\u7847 n m\u7841 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \u432 a v\'e0o trong tay ma t\'e0, m\'ecnh ch\u7881  c\'f2n n\u7855 m hai ba ph\u7847 n. Nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng m\u7841 o hi\u7875 m d\u7909  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\u7897  ra nh\u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7875 m, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  v\u7867  ngo\'e0i, \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ti\u7875 u qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7845 u v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7845 u v\u7899 i qu\u7927 , r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 t\'ednh k\u7871 ; b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'ednh k\u7871 , b\u7883  qu\u7927  t\'ednh k\u7871 , \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e9 g\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd r\u7891 i c\'e0ng k\u7873  s\'e1t v\'e0o c\u7853 u, ch\u7881  v\'e0o b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  \u273 eo tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "Ch\'fa \u273 eo v\u7853 t g\'ec \u273 \'f3? L\u7845 y xu\u7889 ng cho con xem \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7899 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7847 m b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887 , ch\u7853 m r\'e3i, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n t\u7915 ng ch\'fat th\'e1o s\u7907 i d\'e2y \u273 eo b\'ecnh s\u7913  tr\'ean c\u7893  xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 ang s\u7907  b\'ecnh s\u7913  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, cho n\'ean c\u7889  \'fd d\u7909  c\u7853 u th\'e1o b\'f9a h\u7897  m\u7879 nh xu\u7889 ng, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f2n \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 l\u7869  n\'f3 s\u7869  t\'ednh k\u7871  \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u tr\u432 \u7907 t tay l\'e0m r\u417 i b\'ecnh s\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 c\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Cho n\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u432 \u417 n tay, \u273 \u7863 t b\'ecnh s\u7913  v\u7919 ng v\'e0ng \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean tr\'ean b\u7879  c\u7917 a s\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t b\'ecnh s\u7913  r\u7901 i tay, t\'e0 kh\'ed t\'faa ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  v\u7853 t b\'ean ch\'e2n kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng r\u7889 ng \u273 au m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng. C\u7863 p m\u7855 t c\u7911 a n\'f3 tr\u7903  n\'ean \u273 \u7887  ng\u7847 u, hai h\'e0ng huy\u7871 t l\u7879  ch\u7843 y ra, t\u7913  chi b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u k\'e9o d\'e0i, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean o\'e1n \u273 \u7897 c nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m c\uc0\u7911 a n\'f3 tr\u7903  n\'ean v\'f4 c\'f9ng th\'ea l\u432 \u417 ng, \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o m\'e0ng nh\u297  \u273 au nh\u7913 c: "... R\u7889 t cu\u7897 c ng\u432 \u417 i l\'e0 g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ta l\'e0 ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, ch\u7881  v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'ecnh s\u7913 , "Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u th\u7913  kia, l\'e0 d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  tr\u7845 n \'e1p ch\'ednh ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  v\u7853 t l\u7897  ra n\'e9t m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tin.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\'e3ng ph\'ed th\u7901 i c\u417 , l\u7853 p t\u7913 c m\u7897 t c\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e1 v\u7853 t kia ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, du\u7895 i tay c\u7847 m ph\'f9 tri\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m chu\u7849 n b\u7883  d\'e1n l\'ean ng\u7921 c n\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn v\uc0\u7853 t kia h\'f3a th\'e0nh kh\'f3i \u273 en tan bi\u7871 n, l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i d\'e3n ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i, l\u7845 y l\u7841 i b\'ecnh s\u7913  c\u7849 n th\u7853 n \u273 eo l\'ean c\u7893 , m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n pin \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i men theo con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i t\'f2a nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e2y \uc0\u273 en t\u7843 n ra, \'e1nh tr\u259 ng chi\u7871 u xu\u7889 ng m\u7863 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i d\u7889 i. C\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  vi\u7879 c sinh ra \u7903  Tr\'ec gia, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  vi\u7879 c tr\u7901 i sinh t\'e0 kh\'ed qu\u7845 n th\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'e1u \uc0\u273 \'edch t\'f4n c\u7911 a Thi\'ean S\u432  th\u7871  gia, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng tr\u7901 i sinh t\'e0 kh\'ed.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ecnh s\uc0\u7913  ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u, qu\u7843  th\u7853 t c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\'fap c\u7853 u tr\u7845 n \'e1p t\'e0 kh\'ed tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i, tr\'e1nh cho c\u7853 u r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u phi\u7873 n to\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7907  ch\u7891 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 ang \u7903  b\'ean ngo\'e0i ch\u7901  c\u7853 u, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u273 i ra T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m xoa xoa tay ngh\'eanh \u273 \'f3n , s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t d\'f2 h\u7887 i: " Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 ? Gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t xong ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi\'eang nghi\'eang \uc0\u273 \u7847 u, ng\u7849 ng l\'ean n\u7903  m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i ng\'e2y th\u417  v\u7899 i h\u7855 n: "Ch\'fa \u417 i, d\u7851 n con ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, v\u7907  h\u7855 n \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n qu\'e1t to m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, ch\u7881  v\'e0o Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\'ecn h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i nh\u7853 n ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t \u273 \'fang l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean, sau \u273 \'f3 li\u7873 n x\'f4ng l\'ean \u273 \'e1nh c\u7853 u m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7913 c c\'f4 ch\u7859 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao nhi\'eau, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'ecnh \u273 \'f9a qu\'e1 tr\u7899 n, v\'ec v\u7853 y li\'ean t\u7909 c xin l\u7895 i, nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7889 n tr\'e1nh, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tr\'e1nh tho\'e1t h\u7859 n, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n k\'e9o \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean ra \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c an \u7911 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Gi\'e2y l\'e1t sau \uc0\u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean m\u7899 i tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7841 i, gi\u417  tay \'e1ng ch\u7915 ng chi\u7873 u cao m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , n\'f3, c\'e1i m\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7915 a gi\u7843  v\u7901  \u7845 y, gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t xong ch\u432 a?" C\'f4 n\'f3i r\u7845 t nh\u7887 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  s\u7907  qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e2u n\'e0y T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7915 a m\u7899 i h\u7887 i xong, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7841 i \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean h\u7887 i l\u7841 i, kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7847 n n\u7919 a: "Kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , kh\'f4ng l\u7907 i h\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c nh\u432  t\'f4i ngh\u297 , x\u7917  l\'ed xong r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean m\u7899 i th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t h\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'eam \u273 \u7847 u xu\'e2n v\u7851 n c\'f2n r\u7845 t l\u7841 nh, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m th\'fac gi\u7909 c hai ng\u432 \u7901 i mau l\'ean xe r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i ch\u7895  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\'f9ng \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\u7845 p ba c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Khi \u273 \'f3 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\'e0 b\u7841 n th\'e2n nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, h\u7855 n v\'e0 \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean y\'eau s\u7899 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i bao che cho quan h\u7879  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885 . Sau l\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\'e0 \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean h\u7865 n nhau thi v\'e0o tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u7903  c\'f9ng th\'e0nh ph\u7889 , l\'fac \u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'ec ch\u259 m s\'f3c m\u7865  v\'e0 \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ch\u7885 n \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 xa hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\u7903 i v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng b\u7883  ng\u7855 t li\'ean l\u7841 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi t\uc0\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7885 c nghi\'ean c\u7913 u sinh, c\'f2n n\u7917 a n\u259 m n\u7919 a th\'ec t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p. L\'fd t\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7911 a T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m cho t\u7899 i nay v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\'e0 thi v\'e0o tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7843 nh s\'e1t \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u417 ng, gia \u273 \'ecnh gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, sau khi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i tr\u7903  th\'e0nh m\u7897 t c\u7843 nh s\'e1t nh\'e2n d\'e2n; \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean h\u7885 c y khoa ch\'ednh quy, t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p sau b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7897 t n\u259 m, b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 ang th\u7921 c t\u7853 p t\u7841 i m\u7897 t b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n. Th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 th\'e0nh ph\u7889  l\u7899 n, c\'e1c ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n ganh \u273 ua c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gay g\u7855 t, nh\u432 ng \u273 i\u7875 m t\u7889 t l\'e0 cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh. \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m sau khi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p l\u7853 p t\u7913 c k\u7871 t h\'f4n, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  gh\'e9t b\u7887  Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u432 \u7899 ng v\'edu, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t quan t\'e2m c\u7853 u m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n, th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean g\u7885 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 \u259 n c\u417 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai tu\uc0\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7917  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n \u7903  ngo\u7841 i th\'e0nh trao \u273 \u7893 i c\'f4ng t\'e1c, th\u7901 i gian ba th\'e1ng. B\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n \u7903  ngo\u7841 i th\'e0nh n\'e0y chia l\'e0m hai khu: khu \u272 \'f4ng v\'e0 khu T\'e2y, khu T\'e2y l\'e0 khu ch\'ednh, \u273 a s\u7889  c\'e1c b\'e1c s\u297  b\u7879 nh nh\'e2n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'e1m b\u7879 nh \u7903  \u273 \'f3, c\u417  s\u7903  v\u7853 t ch\u7845 t khu \u272 \'f4ng ch\u7911  y\u7871 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\'f2a v\u259 n ph\'f2ng v\'e0 m\u7897 t khu \u273 i\u7873 u tr\u7883  n\u7897 i tr\'fa, kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch gi\u7919  hai khu ch\u7915 ng 20 ph\'fat \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng. Nh\u432 ng th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7879 nh \u273 a s\u7889  v\u7851 n ch\u7885 n v\'e0o n\u7897 i th\'e0nh \u273 i kh\'e1m \u7903  nh\u7919 ng b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n c\'f4ng l\u7853 p n\u7893 i danh, do \u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7879 nh trong vi\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 nhi\u7873 u, khu ch\'ednh c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  cung c\u7845 p gi\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7857 m vi\u7879 n n\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7879 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chuy\u7875 n \u273 \u7871 n khu T\'e2y \u273 i\u7873 u tr\u7883  n\u7897 i tr\'fa l\u7841 i c\'e0ng \'edt h\u417 n, b\u7903 i v\u7853 y n\u417 i n\'e0y th\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u7843 m th\u7845 y qu\u7841 nh qu\u7869 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean v\u7915 a m\u7899 i v\'e0o l\'e0m, ch\u432 a c\'f3 th\'e2m ni\'ean c\u7845 p b\u7853 c g\'ec, l\'e0m vi\u7879 c \u7903  \u273 \'e2y tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \u7905  v\u7845 t v\u7843  h\u417 n v\u7899 i b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n c\'f4 \u273 ang l\'e0m, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng c\'e1ch n\u7897 i th\'e0nh qu\'e1 xa, b\'e1c s\u297  c\'f3 th\'e2m ni\'ean trong vi\u7879 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, v\u7853 y n\'ean h\u7841 n ng\u7841 ch trao \u273 \u7893 i c\'f4ng t\'e1c n\'e0y m\u7899 i r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7847 u c\'f4, b\u7883  ph\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n khu T\'e2y c\'f4ng t\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t tu\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f4 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7855 p x\u7871 p \u273 \u7871 n tr\u7921 c ca \u273 \'eam. \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean s\u7907  l\u7841 nh n\'ean mang ch\u259 n \u273 i nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  qu\'ean \u7903  v\u259 n ph\'f2ng , n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam h\u417 n m\u7897 t gi\u7901  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\u7841 nh kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, \u273 \'e0nh n\'f3i v\u7899 i b\'e1c s\u297  tr\u7921 c c\'f9ng m\u7897 t c\'e2u r\u7891 i ch\u7841 y v\u7873  v\u259 n ph\'f2ng l\u7845 y ch\u259 n. V\u259 n ph\'f2ng c\'f4 l\'e0m vi\u7879 c \u7903  t\u7847 ng b\u7889 n, l\'fac c\u7847 m ch\u259 n kh\'f3a c\u7917 a \u273 i ra ch\u7907 t tho\'e1ng nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng kh\'f3c \u7903  t\u7847 ng tr\'ean, nh\u432 ng t\u7847 ng n\u259 m ch\u7881  l\'e0 ph\'f2ng d\u7909 ng c\u7909  v\'e0 ph\'f2ng l\u432 u tr\u7919 , ngay c\u7843  \u273 \'e8n h\'e0nh lang c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng s\'e1ng, l\'fac n\'e0y l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\'fac n\'e0y c\'f4 \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y h\u417 i run, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 i xem m\'e0 v\u7897 i ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng xu\u7889 ng t\u7847 ng d\u432 \u7899 i\'97\'97 t\'f2a nh\'e0 n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\u361 , \u273 \u7871 n thang m\'e1y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3. K\u7871 t qu\u7843  v\u7915 a ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7847 u h\'e0nh lang \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  k\'e9o l\u7841 i, c\'f4 quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn l\u7841 i, m\u7897 t b\'e9 g\'e1i ch\u7881  cao t\u7899 i th\u7855 t l\u432 ng, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t t\'e1i nh\u7907 t ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7869  h\u7887 i c\'f4: "Ch\u7883  \u417 i em l\u7841 nh qu\'e1, t\u7889 i qu\'e1 em s\u7907  l\u7855 m, ch\u7883  d\u7851 n em ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
