\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng n\'f3 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i, tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7911  nh\'e2n c\u259 n ph\'f2ng c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en \u273 ang n\u7857 m sau l\u432 ng, g\u7855 t gao m\'e0 qu\u7845 n ch\u7863 t m\u7909 c ti\'eau c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'f3ng \uc0\u273 en ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i th\u7913  g\'e2y phi\u7873 n nhi\u7877 u kia, h\u7855 n t\u7841 m th\u7901 i bu\'f4ng ra nh\'e2n lo\u7841 i ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o, h\u417 i n\'e2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, vung tay.\cb1 \
