\f1\b0 \cf2 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau m\uc0\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i d\u7853 y, tr\'ean b\'e0n c\u417 m \u273 \'e3 b\'e0y s\u7861 n \u273 \u7853 u h\u361  v\'e0 b\'e1nh qu\u7849 y, \u273 \u7853 u h\u361  r\u432 \u7899 i n\u432 \u7899 c s\u7889 t, r\u7855 c th\'eam \u7899 t v\'e0 h\u7865 , m\'f9i th\u417 m lan kh\u7855 p. \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 ang c\u7847 m chi\u7871 c radio ki\u7875 u c\u361  ng\u7891 i tr\'ean ban c\'f4ng t\u432 \u7899 i hoa nghe kinh k\u7883 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn b\uc0\u7919 a s\'e1ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i x\u7845 u h\u7893 , m\'ecnh c\'f2n ng\u7911  trong ph\'f2ng, ngo\u7841 i th\'ec \u273 \'e3 t\u7853 p th\u7875  d\u7909 c bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng xong c\'f2n ti\u7879 n th\u7875  mua b\u7919 a s\'e1ng v\u7873 . Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c an \u7911 i, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i c\u417  th\u7875  kh\u7887 e m\u7841 nh, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 c\u361 ng t\u7921  \u273 \u7855 c vui v\u7867  v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng \'f4ng b\'e0 kh\'e1c c\'f9ng trong khu c\u432  x\'e1, th\u7845 y ngo\u7841 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng an t\'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u259 n xong thu d\u7885 n b\'e1t \u273 \u361 a, l\'fac t\u7853 p bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 mua nguy\'ean li\u7879 u v\u7873 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7845 y c\'e0 t\'edm, \u7899 t xanh v\'e0 khoai t\'e2y, \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  c\u417 m tr\u432 a x\'e0o m\u7897 t \u273 \u297 a *\u273 \u7883 a tam ti\'ean, th\'eam m\u7897 t \u273 \u297 a c\'e0 chua tr\u7913 ng. Tr\'ecnh \u273 \u7897  n\u7845 u c\u417 m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng cao, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng, cho n\'ean th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean mua c\u417 m t\u7915  nh\'e0 \u259 n trong tr\u432 \u7901 ng v\u7873  \u259 n c\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i.\cb1 \
