\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u259 n tr\u432 a v\u7899 i \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i xong quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7917 a ng\'e0y, \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  c\u417 m l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi mua c\u417 m v\u7873 . Hi\u7879 n trong nh\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh ngo\u7841 i, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng y\'ean l\'f2ng, mu\u7889 n ch\u259 m s\'f3c ngo\u7841 i nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n, cho n\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7847 n kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 b\u7853 n s\u7869  v\u7873  nh\'e0 \u7903 . Tr\u432 \u7899 c khi v\u7873  h\u432 u \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i c\'f4ng t\'e1c trong nh\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c, m\u7895 i th\'e1ng ti\u7873 n l\u432 \u417 ng h\u432 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ba b\u7889 n ngh\'ecn, ng\'e0y l\u7877  ng\'e0y t\u7871 t \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  ph\'e1t g\u7841 o v\'e0 m\'ec, Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi l\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u th\u7921 c t\u7853 p b\'ean ngo\'e0i, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u \u273 ang h\u7885 c th\u7841 c s\u297 , h\u7885 c ph\'ed kh\'f4ng cao, ti\u7873 n l\u432 \u417 ng th\u7921 c t\u7853 p m\u7895 i th\'e1ng c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t hai ngh\'ecn, g\'f3p l\u7841 i hai \'f4ng ch\'e1u \u273 \u7911  s\u7889 ng \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  nh\u7887  n\'e0y, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac c\u7853 u \u273 i l\'e0m ch\'ednh th\u7913 c r\u7891 i c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  d\u432  d\u7843  h\u417 n ch\'fat \'edt.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i l\'fac \u259 n c\u417 m \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i h\u7887 i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean \'e0, h\'f4m qua sao con v\u7873  mu\u7897 n v\u7853 y, l\'e0m g\'ec sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\uc0\u7871 t ngo\u7841 i l\'e0 l\'e3o \u272 \u7843 ng vi\'ean \u273 \u7843 ng C\u7897 ng S\u7843 n, ki\'ean \u273 \u7883 nh tin t\u432 \u7903 ng v\'e0o ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a duy v\u7853 t c\u7911 a Tri\u7871 t h\u7885 c M\'e1c, b\u7903 i v\'ec c\u259 m gh\'e9t Tr\'ec gia n\'ean \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927  n\'e0y c\u361 ng c\u259 m gh\'e9t, kh\'f4ng \u7911 ng h\u7897  c\u7853 u h\u7885 c nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n ch\u7885 c \'f4ng nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n Tr\'ec gia l\u7841 i t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i th\u7853 t, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i b\u7883 a chuy\u7879 n n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec \u273 \'e2u ngo\u7841 i, con \u273 i \u259 n v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 i ch\u417 i th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i c\u7845 p ba T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m th\u432 \u7901 ng t\u7899 i nh\'e0 ch\u417 i, c\'f3 th\u7875  xem nh\u432  ngo\u7841 i nh\'ecn h\u7855 n l\u7899 n l\'ean, bi\u7871 t r\'f5 t\'ednh c\'e1ch h\u7855 n nghi\'eam ch\u7881 nh, sau khi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p c\'f4ng t\'e1c \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh th\'e0nh gia l\u7853 p nghi\u7879 p, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ch\'ednh \u273 \u7841 o, nghe Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i \u273 i ch\u417 i c\'f9ng h\u7855 n \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i li\u7873 n y\'ean t\'e2m, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i lo l\u7855 ng \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, con xem T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \'e3 k\u7871 t h\'f4n g\u7847 n m\u7897 t n\u259 m r\u7891 i, khi n\'e0o th\'ec con mang \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng v\u7873  cho ngo\u7841 i g\u7863 p? Ngo\u7841 i \u273 i r\u7891 i c\u361 ng y\'ean t\'e2m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7875  \u273 \u361 a xu\u7889 ng, b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  nh\'ecn ngo\u7841 i: "Ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3i linh tinh, s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e ngo\u7841 i c\'f2n t\u7889 t l\u7855 m, n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y l\'e0m g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "Ph\u7843 i th\u7845 y con c\u432 \u7899 i v\u7907  l\u7853 p gia \u273 \'ecnh r\u7891 i m\u7899 i an t\'e2m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. V\u7907  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 l\'e0m \u7903  b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n sao, c\'f3 ai t\u7847 m tu\u7893 i con th\'ec c\u361 ng n\'ean nh\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ngo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng y\'eau c\u7847 u g\'ec, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n t\u7889 t l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ti\uc0\u7871 p n\u7919 a. C\u7853 u hi\u7875 u \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i mu\u7889 n th\'fac h\'f4n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'e1c tr\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7889 i, hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n tu\u7893 i c\u7847 n h\u7889 i h\'f4n. \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i l\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng y\'ean l\'f2ng, cu\u7897 c h\'f4n nh\'e2n th\u7845 t b\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\u7865  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n khi\u7871 n ngo\u7841 i ngh\u7865 n \u7903  h\u7885 ng. C\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  r\'f5 \u7903  tang l\u7877  c\u7911 a m\u7865 , \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7847 u b\u7841 c ti\u7877 n k\u7867  \u273 \u7847 u xanh, lu\'f4n ch\u7843 y n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t l\u7847 m b\u7847 m "L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7845 t quy\u7871 t kh\'f4ng g\u7843  con \u273 i th\'ec t\u7889 t r\u7891 i " .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n c\u361  trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng \u7843 m \u273 \u7841 m, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n khuy\'ean gi\u7843 i ngo\u7841 i n\'f3i: "Ngo\u7841 i y\'ean t\'e2m, vi\u7879 c n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\u7875  g\u7845 p, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7845 t th\'edch h\u7907 p \u273 ang ch\u7901  con."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "Sao l\uc0\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng con g\'e1i v\u7853 y, \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng con trai ph\u7843 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng s\u7869  b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta \u273 o\u7841 t m\u7845 t \u273 \u7845 y." \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, hai m\u7855 t \u273 \u7909 c ng\u7847 u ch\u7907 t \'e1nh l\'ean, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\u7899  t\u7899 i \u273 i\u7873 u g\'ec, trong m\u7855 t hi\u7879 n l\'ean ho\'e0i ni\u7879 m c\'f9ng bi th\u432 \u417 ng, "M\u7865  con tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u361 ng nh\u432  th\u7871 , ta v\'e0 b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i con \u273 \u7873 u c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng chen l\u7901 i, n\'f3i v\u7873  chuy\u7879 n th\u7921 c t\u7853 p r\u7891 i vi\u7879 c h\u7885 c \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, chuy\u7875 n h\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \u7873  t\'e0i n\'e0y. Kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n l\'e0m ngo\u7841 i nh\u7899  t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n x\u432 a kh\u7893  s\u7903  c\u7911 a m\u7865  l\'e0 m\u7897 t nguy\'ean nh\'e2n, c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t nguy\'ean nh\'e2n kh\'e1c c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i v\u7899 i ngo\u7841 i \'97\'97 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i trong l\'f2ng, t\u7915  thu\u7903  bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7871 n rung \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7901 i, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n th\'edch ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n nay \u273 \'e3 b\u7843 y n\u259 m kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p l\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng n\u7855 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7845 t c\u7913  tin t\u7913 c g\'ec v\u7873  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, \'e1i luy\u7871 n nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i d\u7847 n l\'ean men d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng, ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng phai \u273 i, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'e0ng \u7911  c\'e0ng \u273 \u7853 m. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i hay kh\'f4ng, sau khi r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia c\u7853 u v\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 xem nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a hai th\u7871  gi\u7899 i, \u273 \u7901 i n\'e0y c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  g\u7863 p l\u7841 i hay kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 c\u7843  v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 . D\'f9ng th\'e2n ph\u7853 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u b\'e2y gi\u7901 , cho d\'f9 ng\'e0n d\u7863 m xa x\'f4i \u273 i t\'ecm Di\u7879 p gia ch\u7881  s\u7907  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, m\'e0 kha\u777  n\u259 ng cao h\u417 n l\'e0 b\u7883  tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a Di\u7879 p gia ng\u259 n l\u7841 i, v\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\u7853 u c\u7847 m b\'ecnh s\u7913  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, l\u7863 ng l\u7869  gi\u417  l\'ean b\'ean m\'f4i kh\u7869  \u273 \u7909 ng, n\'e9t m\u7863 t tho\'e1ng l\u7897  ch\'fat bi th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho d\'f9 l\'e0 hi\uc0\u7879 n t\u7841 i, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i l\'fac ng\u7911  v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n kh\'ed t\u7913 c v\'e0 v\'f2ng \'f4m c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng trong l\'fac n\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea s\u7869  ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  \u273 ang \u7903  ngay b\'ean c\u7853 u, \'f4m c\u7853 u. Th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f3 l\'fac c\'f2n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y... ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  \u273 ang \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7853 u v\'e0o l\'f2ng, h\'f4n c\u7853 u. Nh\u432 ng sau khi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c hi\u7875 u r\'f5, \u273 \'f3 ch\u7881  l\'e0 t\u432 \u417 \u777 ng t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 v\u7885 ng t\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh m\'e0 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n ch\u7853 m r\'e3i tr\'f4i qua, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng l\u7901 i m\u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u259 n c\u417 m th\'ec t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi. T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\'e0 \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean bi\u7871 t trong nh\'e0 c\u7853 u c\'f2n c\'f3 \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n g\u7885 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 \u259 n \u273 \u7873 u cho c\u7853 u m\u7897 t \'edt \u273 \u7891  \u259 n \u273 \'e3 n\u7845 u s\u7861 n nh\u432  th\u7883 t b\u259 m vi\'ean, th\u7883 t ba ch\u7881  kho, c\'e1nh g\'e0 chi\'ean n\u432 \u7899 c t\u432 \u417 ng, mang v\u7873  ch\u7881  c\u7847 n h\'e2m n\'f3ng l\u7841 i l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  t\u432  \u259 n t\u7889 i xong, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang r\u7917 a b\'e1t chu\'f4ng c\u7917 a ch\u7907 t vang l\'ean, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 i m\u7903  c\u7917 a, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u417 i kinh ng\u7841 c, kh\'f4ng \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y t\'ecm c\u7853 u l\'e0m g\'ec, lau lau tay, nh\u7901  ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u432 a b\u7841 n v\'e0o ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e0 c\'f3 ba ph\'f2ng ng\uc0\u7911 , m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng l\'e0 c\u7911 a \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\'e0 b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c kia, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u7903  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh; m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng l\'e0 c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean; m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng kh\'e1c \u7903  gi\u7919 a l\'e0 c\u7911 a m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Sau khi m\u7865  qua \u273 \u7901 i, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i t\u7915 ng b\u7843 o Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7885 n th\'e0nh ph\'f2ng h\u7885 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i c\u259 n ph\'f2ng hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u l\'e0 \u273 \u7911  r\u7891 i, t\u7915  ch\u7889 i. Cho n\'ean ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u7903  gi\u7919 a b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7875  \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng, ch\u7881  khi n\'e0o qu\'e9t d\u7885 n nh\'e0 c\u7917 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nguy\'ean nh\'e2n l\'e0 v\'ec l\'fac hai m\uc0\u7865  con chuy\u7875 n v\u7873  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p l\'ean c\u7845 p ba, c\u226 \u768 n ph\u7843 i h\u7885 c b\'e0i, trong nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\u7915 a ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m ph\'f2ng h\u7885 c cho c\u7853 u, m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n c\u7889  \'fd ch\u7885 n ph\'f2ng nh\u7887  h\u417 n l\'e0m ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, \u273 \u7875  ph\'f2ng l\u7899 n h\u417 n cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean, b\'ean trong b\'e0y m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u417 n 1m50, t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \u7863 t d\u7921 a v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng, b\'ean kia \u273 \u7863 t b\'e0n s\'e1ch v\'e0 m\u7897 t gi\'e1 s\'e1ch nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean v\'e0o ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, ti\u7879 n tay m\u7903  quy\u7875 n s\'e1ch tr\'ean b\'e0n, tr\'ean trang gi\u7845 y m\u7887 ng \u7889  v\'e0ng v\u7869  tr\u7853 n \u273 \u7891  ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p l\'e0m h\u7855 n qu\'e1ng m\u7855 t, ch\u7919  tri\u7879 n b\'ean c\u7841 nh b\u7913 c tranh c\u361 ng kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t, h\u7855 n mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra m\u7845 y ch\u7919 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "... D\'f9ng c\uc0\u7889 t n\'e0y, nh\u7853 p tim kia ... \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec th\u7871 ?" H\u7855 n l\u7849 m b\u7849 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i qua c\u7845 t s\'e1ch \u273 i: "L\'e0 nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'ean xu\u7889 ng m\u7891  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 D\uc0\u7921 a theo l\u7879  c\u361  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia, v\'ec con trai tr\u432 \u7903 ng k\u7871  th\u7915 a gia nghi\u7879 p, con ch\'e1u khi ra \u7903  ri\'eang c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\u7843 n sao t\u7915  T\'e0ng Th\u432  C\'e1c, l\'fac ch\u7885 n s\'e1ch ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0 ch\u7885 n b\u7845 t k\'ec, ai c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\u7897 i dung s\'e1ch. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\'e0 ch\'e1u \u273 \'edch t\'f4n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean b\u7883  "Ph\'e2n" ra ngo\'e0i, v\u7889 n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i k\u7871  th\u7915 a Tr\'ec gia, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f3 ti\u7873 n l\u7879  nh\u432  v\u7853 y n\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7875  cho c\u7853 u ch\u7885 n b\u7845 t k\'ec ba quy\u7875 n b\u7843 n g\u7889 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7885 n hai quy\u7875 n v\u7915 a l\u7899 n l\u7841 i d\'e0y v\u7899 i m\u7897 t quy\u7875 n tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn v\'f4 c\'f9ng c\u361  n\'e1t. L\u7899 n d\'e0y n\u7897 i dung nhi\u234 \u768 u, c\u361  th\'ec n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f3 ghi ch\'e9p qu\'fd hi\u7871 m, l\'fac \u7845 y c\u7853 u ngh\u297  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, sau khi c\u7847 m \u273 i r\u7891 i m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra hai quy\u7875 n l\u7899 n \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\u7897 t \'edt thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p c\u417  b\u7843 n, ch\'ednh l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  c\u7853 u \u273 ang d\'f9ng, gi\'e1 tr\u7883  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, trong quy\u7875 n s\'e1ch c\u361  th\'ec ghi l\u7841 i r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u b\'ed thu\u7853 t c\u7853 u xem kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fat t\'ecnh c\uc0\u7843 m n\'e0o v\u7899 i Tr\'ec gia, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tham, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 kh\'f4ng th\'e8m \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7891  Tr\'ec gia, l\'fac \u7845 y v\u7851 n mang s\'e1ch \u273 i l\'e0 v\'ec mu\u7889 n h\u7889  l\'e3o Tr\'ec gia m\u7897 t phen, sau khi ra kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n b\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7875  ch\u7845 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ma t\'e0 tuy r\u7857 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  g\'e2y phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c, v\'ec t\u7921  b\u7843 o v\u7879  m\'ecnh c\u7853 u m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u m\'f2 m\u7851 m h\u7885 c hai quy\u7875 n l\u7899 n kia. T\u7915  nh\u7887  c\u7853 u l\u7899 n l\'ean \u7903  Tr\'ec gia, tuy r\u7857 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f3 ai chuy\'ean m\'f4n d\u7841 y c\u7853 u nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng m\u432 a d\u7847 m th\u7845 m l\'e2u h\u7885 c c\u361 ng coi nh\u432  nhanh, kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u \u273 \'e3 n\u7855 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \'edt m\'f4n \u273 \u7841 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i v\uc0\u7873  chuy\u7879 n hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ngo\'e0i vi\u7879 c mang h\u7885  Tr\'ec, c\u7853 u v\'e0 Tr\'ec gia th\u7853 t s\u7921  n\u7917 a \u273 i\u7875 m quan h\u7879  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n. M\'e0 s\u7903  d\u297  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n gi\u7919  h\u7885  Tr\'ec, kh\'f4ng s\u7917 a theo h\u7885  T\'f4 c\u7911 a \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\'e0 m\u7865  ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec l\'fac m\u7865  con c\u7853 u r\u7901 i \u273 i, Tr\'ec gia \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng ngang ng\u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng n\'f3i m\u7865  c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'e1i gi\'e1, m\'e0 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng s\u7917 a h\u7885 , l\'e0 v\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ho\'e0i ni\u7879 m c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'fac ng\u432 \u7901 i kia g\u7885 i t\'ean c\u7853 u, l\u7899 n l\'ean \u7903  Tr\'ec gia l\'e0 Thi\'ean S\u432  th\u7871  gia nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng m\u7897 t l\'f2ng tin r\u7857 ng t\'ean c\u7911 a m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 h\'e0m ngh\u297 a \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f2n l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\'f2n g\u7885 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \'edt nh\u7845 t s\u7869  nh\u7899  r\'f5 t\'ean c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u c\u7853 u s\u7917 a h\u7885 , ng\u432 \u7901 i kia ngay c\u7843  hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u t\'ean g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, v\u7853 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n li\'ean h\u7879  g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nh\'ecn b\u7841 n m\'ecnh c\u7845 t k\u7929  s\'e1ch, nh\u7899  t\u7899 i c\'f4ng lao c\u7913 u v\u7907  m\'ecnh to l\u7899 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean sinh ra t\'e2m k\'ednh s\u7907 , v\'e1i v\'e1i quy\u7875 n s\'e1ch b\u7883  thu l\u7841 i kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quen bi\u7871 t t\u7915  th\u7901 i c\u7845 p ba, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i lu\'f4n h\u7885 c chung m\u7897 t l\u7899 p, c\u361 ng coi nh\u432  m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i duy\'ean ph\u7853 n, quen nhau l\'e2u T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \u7841 i kh\'e1i c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t \'edt chuy\u7879 n nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean\'97\'97 nh\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7889 n \u7903  n\u417 i kh\'e1c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7865  c\u7853 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, nh\u432 ng sau \u273 \'f3 cha c\u7853 u ngo\u7841 i t\'ecnh, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i li\u7873 n ly h\'f4n, m\u7865  c\u7853 u mang theo c\u7853 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R t\'ecm \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i n\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 a. X\'e3 h\u7897 i b\'e2y gi\u7901  chuy\u7879 n h\'f4n nh\'e2n tan v\u7905  nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec l\u7841 , T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 ang h\u7885 c c\u7845 p ba ch\u7881  th\u7893 n th\u7913 c m\u7897 t tho\'e1ng r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n v\u7883  b\u7841 n th\'e2n n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7855 m l\'e0 \u7903  n\u259 m c\u7845 p ba \u273 \'f3, tr\u432 \u7899 c k\u7923  thi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p trung h\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7845 p ba c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n h\u7885 c ngo\u7841 i tr\'fa ho\u7863 c n\u7897 i tr\'fa, h\u7885 c sinh nh\'e0 trong th\'e0nh ph\u7889  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7885 n h\u7885 c ngo\u7841 i tr\'fa, nh\'e0 \u7903  th\u7883  tr\u7845 n c\'e1ch kh\'e1 xa th\'ec h\u7885 c n\u7897 i tr\'fa. T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c v\u7851 n lu\'f4n h\u7885 c ngo\u7841 i tr\'fa, nh\u432 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c k\u7923  thi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p trung h\u7885 c th\u7901 i gian g\u7845 p r\'fat, v\'ec kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n l\u417 i l\u7887 ng, l\'e3ng ph\'ed th\u7901 i gian, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\'e0n b\u7841 c xong r\u7891 i xin h\u7885 c n\u7897 i tr\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\'e1ch k\u7923  thi \u272 \u7841 i H\u7885 c ch\u7915 ng m\u7897 t th\'e1ng, m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\u7885  m\u432 \u7901 i r\u432 \u7905 i t\u7889 i, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7921  h\u7885 c bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i xong chu\u7849 n b\u7883  tr\u7903  v\u7873  k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 t\u7855 m r\u7917 a r\u7891 i ng\u7911 . \u272 i\u7873 u h\'f2a trong ph\'f2ng h\u7885 c b\u7883  h\u7887 ng, hai ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 tr\u7901 i n\'f3ng l\u7841  th\u432 \u7901 ng, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m h\u7885 c sinh chen l\u7845 n trong l\u7899 p h\u7885 c ba ti\u7871 ng, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u ng\u7897 p ra m\u7897 t th\'e2n m\u7891  h\'f4i kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, ph\'f2ng h\u7885 c b\u7883  gi\'f3 th\u7893 i c\'e0ng th\'eam kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 v\'f4 c\'f9ng tr\'f9ng h\uc0\u7907 p ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m k\'fd t\'fac x\'e1 h\u7871 t n\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 ang b\u7883  \'e1p l\u7921 c h\u7885 c t\u7853 p b\u7913 c b\'e1ch, tinh th\u7847 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng, v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 l\'ean k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch xong xu\'f4i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7883  tr\u7903  ng\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, trong l\'f2ng kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u nh\u432  c\'f3 c\u7887  d\u7841 i m\u7885 c l\'ean, v\u7889 n ch\u7881  \u273 ang b\u7843 y t\'e1m ph\u7847 n mu\u7889 n t\u7855 m, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh m\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7847 n mu\u7889 n t\u7855 m, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\u7871 u \u273 \'eam nay kh\'f4ng t\u7855 m th\'ec s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i ng\u7911  c\u361 ng ng\u7911  kh\'f4ng ngon.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  sau h\u7855 n ng\u7851 m l\u7841 i l\'fac \u7845 y t\'e2m l\'fd v\'e0 h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 i\'ean r\u7891  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\'f3 l\u7869  ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 m b\'e1o s\u7869  g\u7863 p t\'e0.\cb1 \
