\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y th\'f4ng b\'e1o h\u7871 t n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m: "T\'f4i nh\u7899  l\'e0 t\u7915  ngo\'e0i t\u432 \u7901 ng ph\'eda t\'e2y tr\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh \u273 i ra ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n n\u259 m ph\'fat c\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'e0 t\u7855 m c\'f4ng c\u7897 ng, hay l\'e0 ch\'fang ta \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f3 t\u7855 m \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nghe xong l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd. Tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\'f3 g\'e1c c\u7893 ng, nh\u432 ng h\u7847 u nh\u432  t\u7845 t c\u7843  nam sinh \u273 \u7873 u nh\u7843 y v\u432 \u7907 t t\u432 \u7901 ng ph\'eda t\'e2y s\'e2n th\u7875  d\u7909 c, chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\'e0 n\'f3i c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng t\uc0\u7855 m m\u7903  \u273 \u7871 n 11h \u273 \'eam, l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \u7871 n th\'ec \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p t\u7899 i th\u7901 i gian \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a, c\'f3 v\'e0i nh\'f3m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang \u273 i ra. Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i giao ti\u7873 n, nh\'e2n vi\'ean tr\'f4ng c\u7917 a \u273 \u432 a ch\'eca kh\'f3a t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o cho b\u7885 n h\u7885 , nh\u7855 c nh\u7903 : "Nhanh l\'ean \u273 \u7845 y, s\u7855 p h\u7871 t gi\u7901  r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m, b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng \u273 \u7883 nh t\u7855 m nhanh, h\u417 n n\u7919 a b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7871 u c\'f3 kh\'e1ch ch\u432 a t\u7855 m xong th\'ec s\u7869  \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a mu\u7897 n n\u259 m m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f3 th\u7875  k\u7883 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng t\uc0\u7855 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\'e2y v\'f4 c\'f9ng s\u417  s\'e0i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\'e0 t\u7855 m c\'f4ng c\u7897 ng m\'e0 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  c\'f3 \u7903  ph\u432 \u417 ng B\u7855 c hai m\u432 \u417 i ba m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c, b\u7889 n ph\'eda \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t d\'e3y v\'f2i sen, ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\u7875  t\u7855 m r\u7845 t \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'f9ng. V\u7873  sau \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n nh\'e0 \u7903  c\u7843 i thi\u7879 n, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u t\u7855 m \u7903  nh\'e0, lo\u7841 i nh\'e0 t\u7855 m c\'f4ng c\u7897 ng n\'e0y d\u7847 n d\u7847 n tuy\u7879 t t\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7885 n h\u7885  h\u7885 c l\u7899 p 12 tr\u432 \u7901 ng chuy\u7875 n \u273 \u7871 n *t\'e2n khu c\u7911 a th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, t\'e2n khu t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i xa, nghe n\'f3i l\'e0 khu ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n tr\u7885 ng \u273 i\u7875 m trong t\u432 \u417 ng lai, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n, d\'e2n c\u432  ch\u7911  y\u7871 u v\u7851 n t\u7853 p trung \u7903  nh\u7919 ng khu c\u361  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia trong th\'e0nh ph\u7889  khi\u7871 n cho n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn c\'f3 v\u7867  h\u7867 o l\'e1nh. C\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i lao \u273 \u7897 ng t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7871 n v\'ec ti\u7871 t ki\u7879 m ti\u7873 n thu\'ea nh\'e0 n\'ean \u7903  g\u7847 n n\u417 i n\'e0y, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng tan t\u7847 m s\u7869  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y t\u7855 m r\u7917 a gi\u7843 i t\u7887 a m\u7879 t m\u7887 i; h\u417 n n\u7919 a n\u417 i n\'e0y g\u7847 n nh\'e0 ga v\'e0 b\u7871 n xe, \u273 \u7871 n m\'f9a h\'e8 kh\'e1ch t\u7841 m d\u7915 ng ch\'e2n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng t\u7899 i t\u7855 m qua, cho n\'ean quanh tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c c\'f2n c\'f3 v\'e0i nh\'e0 t\u7855 m c\'f4ng c\u7897 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y. C\'e1ch tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c g\u7847 n nh\u7845 t l\'e0 nh\'e0 t\u7855 m c\'f3 t\u7915  l\'e2u nh\u7845 t, thi\u7871 t b\u7883  c\u361  n\'e1t nh\u7845 t, c\u361 ng r\u7867  nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
