\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n t\u7855 m r\u7917 a qua loa r\u7891 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7855 t b\u7867  ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh nhi\u7873 u, c\u7903 i qu\u7847 n \'e1o xong c\u7847 m \u273 \u7891  v\u7885 t v\'e0o. L\'fac b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i v\'e0o c\'f2n c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang t\u7855 t v\'f2i sen \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i. Di\u7879 n t\'edch ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m kh\'f4ng coi l\'e0 nh\u7887 , tr\u7915  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a \u273 i kia th\'ec ch\u7881  c\'f3 l\u7867  t\u7867  hai ba ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7899 i v\'f2i sen, h\u417 n n\u7919 a nh\'ecn c\'f3 v\u7867  c\u361 ng s\u7855 p t\u7855 m xong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'ednh gi\uc0\u7919 a nh\'e0 t\u7855 m tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, ph\'eda g\u7847 n b\'ean trong m\u7897 t lo\u7841 t \u273 \'e8n b\u7883  h\u7887 ng, ch\u7853 p ch\u7901 n l\'fac s\'e1ng l\'fac t\u7889 i, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7885 n hai v\'f2i sen c\'f2n d\'f9ng t\u7889 t, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7855 m r\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7855 m kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng mi\u7879 ng, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m mi\u7879 ng r\u7843 nh r\u7895 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , t\'f4i k\u7875  cho c\u7853 u nghe m\u7897 t c\'e2u \u273 \u7889  \u273 \u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\'ean m\u7841 ng nh\'e9: c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t nh\'e0 t\u7855 m c\'f9ng lo\u7841 i nh\u432  ch\'fang ta \u273 ang d\'f9ng, khi ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 \u273 i v\'e0o tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y trong b\u7891 n t\u7855 m c\'f3 ba ng\u432 \u7901 i, d\u432 \u7899 i v\'f2i sen c\'f3 n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i, trong l\'fac c\u7853 u ta t\u7855 m l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\'eam b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n, c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ra kh\u7887 i b\u7891 n t\u7855 m, m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7855 t v\'f2i sen \u273 i ra, c\u7853 u ta v\'e0 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t ti\u7871 n v\'e0o b\u7891 n t\u7855 m, l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u ta ng\u7891 i trong b\u7891 n ng\u7855 m nh\'ecn b\u7889 n ph\'eda, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\'f2n c\'f3 b\u7843 y ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7899 i v\'f2i sen. C\u7853 u n\'f3i xem nh\u432  th\u7871  c\'f3 \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat: "Nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y nh\'e9, t\'ednh theo l\u432 \u7907 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n. Trong ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m v\u7889 n c\'f3 ch\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i, ba ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i, b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n, v\u7853 y l\'e0 c\'f3 m\u432 \u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i. Trong b\u7891 n t\u7855 m v\u7889 n c\'f3 ba ng\u432 \u7901 i, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i, ba ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n, v\u7853 y c\'f3 b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'fac \u273 \'f3 d\u432 \u7899 i v\'f2i sen ph\u7843 i c\'f3 c\'f3 s\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7899 i \u273 \'fang, t\'ednh sai r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nh\u7841 t nh\u7869 o n\'f3i: "Th\'ec \u273 \'e2y v\u7889 n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n ma m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'e1nh m\uc0\u7855 t ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "\u272 \'eam h\'f4m khuya kho\u7855 t \u7903  n\u417 i hoang v\u7855 ng, kh\'f4ng n\'ean n\'f3i m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927  h\u7907 p c\u7843 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7841 o n\'f3i: "Chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y v\u7915 a nghe \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t l\'e0 b\u7883 a m\'e0, \u273 \'e2u ai r\u7843 nh \u273 i t\u7855 m c\'f2n \u273 \u7871 m s\u7889  ng\u432 \u7901 i k\u297  v\u7853 y ch\u7913 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'fac b\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n l\u7841 i c\'f3 ba ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7855 m xong thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c \u273 i ra, c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y r\'f5 ti\u7871 ng m\u7903  \u273 \'f3ng t\u7911  \u7903  gian thay \u273 \u7891  ph\'eda ngo\'e0i, r\u7845 t nhanh, nh\u7919 ng \'e2m thanh n\'e0y c\u361 ng bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'fac gi\uc0\u7909 c n\'f3i: "T\u7855 m nhanh l\'ean, \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3i n\u7919 a, ch\u7881  c\'f2n hai b\u7885 n m\'ecnh th\'f4i \u273 \u7845 y, nh\'e2n vi\'ean s\u7855 p t\u7899 i \u273 u\u7893 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng sao \u273 \'e2u, c\'f2n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0o tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\'fang ta m\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n b\u297 u m\'f4i ch\u7881 a ch\u7881 a ra sau l\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn, qu\u7843  nhi\'ean th\u7845 y ph\'eda sau m\'ecnh c\'e1ch hai v\'f2i sen c\'f2n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang m\u7903  n\u432 \u7899 c quay l\u432 ng ra t\u7855 m r\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7921 c gi\'e1c c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, l\'fac \u273 i v\'e0o ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 h\'ecnh nh\u432  kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i. C\u7853 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng, l\'fac \u273 i v\'e0o c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, v\u7915 a v\'e0o t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 v\u7897 i t\'ecm v\'f2i sen t\u7855 m cho nhanh r\u7891 i, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i t\'f4i v\u7915 a g\u7897 i \u273 \u7847 u v\u7915 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, m\u7855 t nh\u7855 m su\u7889 t n\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng lu\'f4n h\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7863 t v\u7873  ph\'eda T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, quay l\u432 ng v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n t\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o, hay l\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng v\u7889 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  \u273 \'f3, ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\'ecnh l\'fac \u273 i v\'e0o kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua ph\'eda sau, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng v\u7851 n \u273 \u432 a l\u432 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u, hai tay xoa t\'f3c, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang g\u7897 i \u273 \u7847 u, n\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915  v\'f2i sen ch\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng ng\u259 n c\'e1ch t\u7847 m nh\'ecn l\'e0m c\u7853 u nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng r\'f5.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y gian ngo\'e0i truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng g\u7885 i l\u7899 n c\u7911 a nh\'e2n vi\'ean: "M\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901  n\u259 m ph\'fat r\u7891 i, s\u7889  m\u432 \u7901 i t\'e1m m\u432 \u7901 i ch\'edn nhanh l\'ean, ch\u7881  c\'f2n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e1c c\u7853 u th\'f4i \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn s\u7889  th\u7867  tr\'ean tay m\'ecnh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7889  m\u432 \u7901 i t\'e1m, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m s\u7889  m\u432 \u7901 i ch\'edn.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng nh\'e2n vi\'ean l\u7849 m b\u7849 m t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n c\'f9ng ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n lo\u7865 t xo\u7865 t r\u7901 i \u273 i lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng truy\u7873 n v\'e0o: "Ph\u7843 i \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a r\u7891 i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ra th\'ec kh\'f4ng v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u432 \u7901 i khan m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, h\u7841  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'e1c c\u7893 ng nh\u7899  l\u7897 n ha?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, "H\u7855 n" v\u7851 n duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \u432 a l\u432 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda b\u7885 n h\u7885 , c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u, \u273 \u7875  tay tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u ch\'e0 x\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o v\u7899 i b\u7841 n m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u c\u7853 u \u273 o\'e1n kh\'f4ng sai, kia h\u7859 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'e9o T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, th\'ec th\u7847 m n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y l\u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ta v\u7915 a n\'f3i kh\'f4ng? ' s\u7889  m\u432 \u7901 i t\'e1m m\u432 \u7901 i ch\'edn nhanh l\'ean, ch\u7881  c\'f2n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e1c c\u7853 u th\'f4i \u273 \u7845 y', \u7903  \u273 \'e2y ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, n\'f3 l\'e0 \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u7907 c linh, n\'f3 kh\'f4ng ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (\uc0\u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u7907 c linh: h\u7891 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t b\u7883  h\u7841 n ch\u7871  ph\u7841 m vi ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng, b\u7883  tr\'f3i bu\u7897 c. Lo\u7841 i vong linh n\'e0y c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u o\'e1n ni\u7879 m kh\'f4ng ti\'eau n\'ean tr\u7903  th\'e0nh \'e1c linh)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7907  h\'e3i, nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t: "Tr\u7915  phi n\'f3 m\u432 \u7907 n th\'e2n ph\u7853 n m\u7897 t trong hai ch\'fang ta \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7883  d\u7885 a, Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i c\u7921 c k\'ec th\u7853 t, h\u7855 n ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7907  \u273 \u7871 n n\u7893 i da g\'e0, l\'f4ng t\u417  b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u d\u7921 ng \u273 \u7913 ng. H\u7855 n chuy\u7875 n h\u432 \u7899 ng t\u7847 m m\u7855 t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'ean kia, run r\u7849 y n\'f3i: "... M\u432 \u7907 n, m\u432 \u7907 n th\u7871  n\'e0o ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, im l\uc0\u7863 ng nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang suy ngh\u297  g\'ec \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7917 a b\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7853 u b\u7883  che b\u7903 i b\'f3ng t\u7889 i trong ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m, \'e1nh m\u7855 t r\u7845 t b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, nh\u432 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nh\'ecn th\u7845 y l\u7841 i ho\u7843 ng s\u7907 , kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a tay ra tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t c\u7853 u qu\u417  qu\u417 : "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t, kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "... C\u7853 u l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7865  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, ra hi\u7879 u \u273 \u7915 ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7893  s\u7919 a t\u7855 m nha \u273 am m\'e0u xanh nh\u7841 t ra l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay tr\'e1i, tay ph\u7843 i n\u7855 m c\'e1nh tay T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, l\u7845 y s\u7919 a t\u7855 m c\u7845 p t\u7889 c v\u7869  m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c ph\'f9 l\'ean mu b\'e0n tay h\u7855 n, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng r\u7845 t nhanh d\u7863 n d\'f2: "Ch\'fa \'fd m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7875  b\u7883  qu\u7865 t m\u7845 t. C\u7853 u ra th\u7859 ng c\u7917 a tr\u7889 n \u273 i lu\'f4n \u273 i, th\u7913  kia c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\'ean tay c\u7853 u c\'f3 \u273 \u7891 , \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\'f2n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7885 n, n\'f3 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng m\u7841 o hi\u7875 m \u273 u\u7893 i theo c\u7853 u. Nghe t\'f4i, \u273 i mau \u273 i \u273 \u7915 ng b\u7853 n t\'e2m t\'f4i, t\'f4i c\'f3 c\'e1ch, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ch\'fang ta ai c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u417  b\u7855 p to\'e0n th\'e2n b\u7903 i v\'ec s\u7907  h\'e3i m\'e0 c\u259 ng c\u7913 ng, mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng \'e9p bu\u7897 c ch\'ednh m\'ecnh tr\u7845 n \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7841 i, tuy r\u7857 ng v\u7851 n ch\u432 a r\'f5 t\'ecnh h\'ecnh l\'fac n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n tin l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean. V\'ec v\u7853 y g\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, c\u7889  gi\u7919  v\u7867  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7845 y T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a, tim v\u7915 a th\u7843  l\u7887 ng l\u7841 i treo l\'ean. C\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u7899 n l\u7841 nh l\u432 \u7899 t qua sau l\u432 ng, l\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1 quen thu\u7897 c, b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  \u273 \'f3 nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u bi\u7871 t th\u7913  kia \u273 ang theo d\'f5i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3 mu\uc0\u7889 n \u273 i, h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t c\u7853 u r\u7891 i, n\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 a tay kh\u7869  vu\u7889 t ve b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, n\u7895  l\u7921 c ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  n\u7895 i s\u7907  trong l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi c\'f2n nh\uc0\u7887  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  h\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n. C\'f4 h\u7891 n o\'e1n qu\u7927  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng e s\u7907  t\'e0 kh\'ed trong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u m\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n, nh\u432 ng l\u7879  qu\u7927  v\'e0 \'e1c qu\u7927  b\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7853 u l\'e0 ch\'e1u \u273 \'edch t\'f4n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia m\'e0 c\u7889  \'fd l\'e0m h\u7841 i th\'ec kh\'f4ng. Ch\'fang \u7849 n n\'fap trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i, kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng t\'ecm c\'e1ch \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u v\'e0o ch\u7895  ch\u7871 t. Cho n\'ean \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  b\u7843 n n\u259 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n s\u7907  nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u y\u7871 u nh\u432 \u7907 c b\u7845 t l\u7921 c nh\u7845 t, trong v\'f4 s\u7889  \u273 \'eam kinh s\u7907  \u273 an xen, l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \u273 \'e3 \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c d\u7895  d\'e0nh, an \u7911 i, c\u7853 u m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  an t\'e2m m\'e0 ch\'ecm v\'e0o gi\u7845 c ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'e2ng b\'ecnh s\uc0\u7913  l\'ean kh\u7869  h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i, l\u7845 y xu\u7889 ng qu\u7845 n l\'ean tay ph\u7843 i, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\u7845 y s\u7919 a t\u7855 m, r\u7845 t nhanh v\u7869  m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c ph\'f9 tr\u7915  t\'e0 l\'ean l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay tr\'e1i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ecnh s\uc0\u7913  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u. C\u7853 u r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia hai n\u259 m, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng thu \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7917 a \u273 i\u7875 m tin t\u7913 c v\u7873  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, c\'e1c gia t\u7897 c Thi\'ean s\u432  \u273 \u7873 u t\u7921  x\u432 ng l\'e0 *\u273 \u7841 i \u7849 n vu th\u7883 , ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng mu\u7889 n t\'ecm t\u417 \u769 i c\u432 \u777 a l\'e0 ng\'e0n v\u7841 n kh\'f3 kh\u259 n, khi\u7871 n cho c\u7853 u ngay c\u7843  m\u7897 t l\'e1 th\u432  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng g\u7917 i \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Ngay t\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u cho r\u7857 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean m\'ecnh, l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m m\u7899 i l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  g\u7917 i \u273 \u7871 n, v\u7915 a \u273 \'fang v\'e0o ng\'e0y m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m th\'e1ng Gi\'eang \'e2m l\u7883 ch, sinh nh\u7853 t m\u432 \u7901 i t\'e1m tu\u7893 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (*c\'e2u \uc0\u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7911  l\'e0 'ti\u7875 u \u7849 n vu d\'e3, \u273 \u7841 i \u7849 n vu th\u7883 ': ti\u7875 u \u7849 n vu th\u7883  \'fd n\'f3i nh\u7919 ng \u7849 n s\u297  th\u7845 u hi\u7875 u h\u7891 ng tr\u7847 n \u7849 n c\u432  trong n\'fai ch\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  l\'e0 h\'ecnh th\u7913 c \u7903  \u7849 n m\'e0 th\'f4i, nh\u7901  ngo\u7841 i c\u7843 nh xung quanh m\'e0 qu\'ean \u273 i th\u7871  s\u7921 ; c\'f2n th\u7921 c s\u7921  \u273 \u7841 t t\u7899 i c\u7843 nh gi\u7899 i cao th\'ec ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7889 ng trong th\'e0nh ph\u7889  tr\u7847 n t\u7909 c m\'e0 v\u7851 n g\u7841 t b\u7887  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c phi\u7873 n nhi\u7877 u, t\u7921  \u273 \u7855 c vui c\u432 \u7901 i.)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\'e0 \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'f3ng g\'f3i \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, b\'ean trong ch\u7881  c\'f3 b\'ecnh s\u7913  n\'e0y v\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7901  gi\u7845 y, tr\'ean gi\u7845 y d\'f9ng n\'e9t ch\u7919  quen thu\u7897 c vi\u7871 t m\u7845 y ch\u7919  \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n: "Cho b\u7843 o b\u7889 i c\u7911 a anh, ph\u7843 i mang b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i". Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7847 m l\'ean r\u7891 i li\u7873 n tr\'e2n qu\'fd kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n b\u7887  xu\u7889 ng, c\u7847 m trong tay ng\u7855 m nh\'ecn t\u7881  m\u7881 , m\u7897 t kh\u7855 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\u7905  r\u7901 i tay, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n b\'ecnh s\u7913  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\'e2u v\'e0o m\u7897 t s\u7907 i d\'e2y m\'e0u \u273 en li\u7873 n v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 eo l\'ean c\u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'f3n qu\'e0 n\'e0y c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng g\'ec, \u273 eo v\'e0i ng\'e0y r\u7891 i m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n hi\u7879 u qu\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c kia Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  c\u417  th\u7875  \u7903  n\u417 i c\'f4ng c\u7897 ng, t\u7855 m \u7903  nh\'e0 t\u7855 m c\'f4ng c\u7897 ng l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m, m\'f9a h\'e8 lu\'f4n m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \u7853 m m\'e0u, b\u7903 i v\'ec tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c v\'e0 tr\'ean hai vai c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u d\'f9ng b\'fat son v\u7869  ph\'f9 tr\u7845 n t\'e0 d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  tr\u7845 n \'e1p t\'e0 kh\'ed trong c\u417  th\u7875 , n\u7871 u b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c nh\'ecn th\u7845 y nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u7843 m th\u7845 y v\'f4 c\'f9ng qu\'e1i d\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec gia kh\'f4ng ai quan t\'e2m c\uc0\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7901 i duy nh\u7845 t ch\u259 m nom c\u7853 u l\'e0 m\u7865  ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 quy\u7873 n l\'ean ti\u7871 ng \u7903  Tr\'ec gia, ph\'f9 tr\u7845 n t\'e0 n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 do ng\u432 \u7901 i kia gi\'fap c\u7853 u v\u7869  l\'ean. B\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7897 t th\'e1ng v\u7869  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, khi c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u7903  Tr\'ec gia, m\u7895 i ch\u7911  nh\u7853 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kia s\u7869  v\u7869  cho c\u7853 u. Sau khi r\u7901 i \u273 i Tr\'ec gia, Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u h\u7885 c t\u7921  v\u7869  cho m\'ecnh, sau l\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng v\u7899 i t\u7899 i n\'ean kh\'f4ng v\u7869  n\u7919 a, c\'f2n l\u7841 i ba \u273 i\u7875 m c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7845 n \'e1p h\u7847 u h\u7871 t t\'e0 kh\'ed trong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7889 n ch\u7881  coi \u273 eo b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u432  v\'f2ng c\u7893  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7903 i ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7863 ng qu\'e0 n\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t qu\'fd tr\u7885 ng, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n c\u7853 u ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7845 t ph\'e0m c\u7911 a b\'ecnh s\u7913  n\'e0y\'97\'97 n\'f3 kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7845 n \'e1p t\'e0 kh\'ed trong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u m\'e0 ma t\'e0 b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n n\'f3.\cb1 \
