\cf2 \cb3 H\'f4m nay c\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  ph\u7843 i nh\u7901  b\'ecnh s\u7913  n\'e0y c\u7913 u m\'ecnh m\u7897 t m\u7841 ng r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7855 c \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u7907 c linh m\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2u, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\'f3 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng b\u7883  t\'e0 kh\'ed tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh d\u7885 a l\'f9i. Nh\u432 ng lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u7907 c linh c\'f3 th\u7875  xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n l\'fac 12h \u273 \'eam, hi\u7879 n th\'e0nh h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u432 a l\u432 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda th\u7913  kia, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i n\'f3, d\u7883 ch chuy\u7875 n bi\'ean \u273 \u7897  nh\u7887  ra b\'ean ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i v\'f2i sen "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" kia v\u7851 n \u273 ang g\u7897 i \u273 \u7847 u, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i t\u7855 m, t\u7915 ng ch\'fat xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn "M\uc0\u7863 t" n\'f3, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m chuy\u7875 n t\u7847 m m\u7855 t, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7913  kia quay h\u7859 n ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, l\u7897  ra ch\'ednh di\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch v\'f4 h\u7891 n, ng\u361  quan m\u7901  nh\u7841 t, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u432 \u7907 ng g\u7895 , m\u7901  nh\u7841 t \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh c\u7911 a n\'f3. Trong ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n ch\u7853 p ch\u7901 n m\u7901  t\u7889 i, chi\u7871 u ra kho\u7843 ng s\'e1ng loang l\u7893 , d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh s\'e1ng l\u7901  m\u7901 , th\u7913  kia h\'ecnh nh\u432 ... \u273 ang c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f3e mi\uc0\u7879 ng nh\u432  kh\u7855 c g\u7895  gi\u417  l\'ean, nh\u7871 ch \u273 \'f4i m\'f4i \u273 \u7887  t\u432 \u417 i nh\u432  t\u432 \u7907 ng trong ch\'f9a, to\'e9t mi\u7879 ng c\u432 \u7901 i, tuy r\u7857 ng tr\'ean m\u7863 t th\u7913  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t tia huy\u7871 t s\u7855 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3 ch\uc0\u7853 m r\'e3i di chuy\u7875 n v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e0n nh\'e0 t\uc0\u7855 m \u273 ang l\'eanh l\'e1ng n\u432 \u7899 c d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh v\u361 ng b\'f9n s\'e2u, l\'e0m c\u7853 u l\'fan s\'e2u trong \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y h\u417 i kh\'e1c so v\u7899 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c khi r\u417 i v\'e0o \u273 \u7847 m l\u7847 y c\'e0ng gi\'e3y d\u7909 a c\'e0ng ch\'ecm xu\u7889 ng nhanh, n\'f3 gi\u7889 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7883  qu\u7927  \'e1p gi\u432 \u7901 ng h\u417 n, r\'f5 r\'e0ng \'fd th\u7913 c v\u7851 n t\u7881 nh t\'e1o nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n c\u417  th\u7875 , kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, n\u7897 i t\'e2m r\u7845 t ho\u7843 ng lo\u7841 n, \'fd th\u7913 c ra s\u7913 c gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f3 n\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915  ph\'eda tr\'ean \u273 \u7893  xu\u7889 ng, v\'f2i sen c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'f3ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o l\u7841 i m\u7903 . N\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng d\u7897 i l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u, c\u361 ng l\'e0m ph\'f9 tr\u7915  t\'e0 trong l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay b\u7883  r\u7917 a tr\'f4i g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u tr\u417  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn s\u7907 i d\'e2y \u273 en qu\u7845 n tr\'ean tay m\'ecnh d\u432 \u7899 i t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a d\'f2ng n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7883  tu\u7897 t ra, t\u7915 ng v\'f2ng qu\u7845 n r\u7901 i ra, tay c\u7853 u bu\'f4ng th\'f5ng \u7903  \u273 \'f3, \u273 \u7897 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7897 ng, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng d\u432 \u7899 i t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a tr\u7885 ng l\u7921 c, b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  kh\u7869  "\u272 inh" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u417 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong kho\uc0\u7843 nh kh\u7855 c \u273 \'f3, nu\u7889 i ti\u7871 c th\u7853 m ch\'ed \u273 \'e3 l\u7845 n \'e1t n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 h\u7841  xu\u7889 ng theo b\'ecnh s\u7913 , trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t, t\'e0 kh\'ed tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p quanh th\'e2n. M\'e0 ch\u7881  trong m\u7897 t kh\u7855 c n\'e0y, l\'fac ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean th\u7913  kia \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi ho\uc0\u7863 c, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  th\u7913  kia s\u7907  t\'e0 kh\'ed c\u7911 a m\'ecnh n\'ean bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t? Kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u432 a th\u7875  c\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng, th\u7913  kia ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n ch\u432 a r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u ch\u7907 t c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7855 t c\'e1 ch\'e2n ph\u7843 i l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915  t\u7915  li\u7871 c xu\u7889 ng, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay \u273 ang n\u7855 m ch\'e2n ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u, th\u7913  kia \u273 ang n\u7857 m r\u7841 p tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean nh\'ecn c\u7853 u...\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i tr\u432 \u7899 c nhanh ch\'f3ng m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o, sau \u273 \'f3 v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng y\'ean l\'f2ng, t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'e1c c\u7917 a r\u7891 i t\'ednh to\'e1n quay tr\u7903  l\u7841 i c\u7913 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean. H\u7855 n ngh\u297  kh\'f4ng n\'ean n\'f3i ra chuy\u7879 n ma qu\'e1i g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'e1c c\u7917 a ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tin, b\'e8n n\'f3i d\u7889 i b\'ean trong c\'f3 tr\u7897 m v\'e0o l\u7845 y c\u7855 p \u273 \u7891  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885 , hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i b\u7841 n h\u7855 n \u273 ang ng\u259 n t\'ean tr\u7897 m kh\'f4ng cho \u273 i, c\'f2n h\u7855 n \u273 i ra t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7895  tr\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'e1c c\u7917 a v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng tin, ki\'ean tr\'ec n\'f3i m\'ecnh v\u7851 n lu\'f4n tr\'f4ng coi \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\'f3 ai \u273 i v\'e0o, l\u7841 i c\'e0ng mu\u7889 n t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 i v\'e0o x\'e1c nh\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\'e3i ch\u432 a ra c\u361 ng b\u7845 t an, c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n quay l\u7841 i xem t\'ecnh h\'ecnh, b\'e8n c\u226 \u768 m \u273 i\'ea\u803 n thoa\u803 i g\u7885 i cho m\u7897 t huynh \u273 \u7879  t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, nh\u7901  c\u7853 u ta b\'e1o c\u7843 nh s\'e1t, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 i theo ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'e1c c\u7917 a v\'e0o nh\'e0 t\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng t\uc0\u7855 m v\'f4 c\'f9ng y\'ean t\u297 nh, ch\u7881  c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7887  gi\u7885 t, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m li\u7871 c m\u7855 t li\u7873 n th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang d\u7921 a tr\'ean t\u432 \u7901 ng, m\u7855 t nh\u7855 m l\u7841 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 ng\u7845 t \u273 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y tim h\u7855 n l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7897 p m\u7897 t c\'e1i, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7855 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 ph\u7843 i v\'ec b\u7843 o v\u7879  m\'ecnh m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p b\u7845 t tr\u7855 c hay kh\'f4ng. H\u417 n n\u7919 a h\u7855 n ph\u7843 i th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n, h\u7855 n r\u7845 t s\u7907 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\u7841 i g\u7847 n ki\u7875 m tra xem b\u7841 n m\'ecnh c\'f3 sao hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n s\u7907 , s\u7907  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 h\u7855 n g\u7885 i t\u7881 nh, m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'96 h\u7843 o b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u s\u7899 m t\u7889 i g\u7855 n b\'f3 su\u7889 t c\u7845 p ba, m\'e0 l\'e0 th\u7913  m\u432 \u7907 n th\'e2n ph\u7853 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7875  \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i nh\u432  l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng n\u7895 i lo cho b\u7841 n v\u7851 n chi\u7871 n th\u7855 ng n\u7895 i s\u7907 , T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 i t\u7899 i v\u7895  v\u7895  vai Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 ? T\u7881 nh t\u7881 nh, t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i mau, c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i!"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n g\u7885 i t\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0i l\u7847 n, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7899 i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7903  m\u7855 t. \'c1nh m\u7855 t thanh minh, l\'fac nh\'ecn h\u7855 n c\u361 ng l\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c quen thu\u7897 c. T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ch\u7853 m r\'e3i th\u7903  ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i, kh\'f4ng sai, \u273 \'e2y v\u7851 n l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7913  kia \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean l\u7841 i l\'e0 nh\'ecn xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t. C\u7853 u d\'f2 tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t m\u7897 t v\'f2ng, r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 ang t\'ecm v\u7853 t g\'ec \u273 \'f3, sau khi kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7897  r\'f5 v\u7867  ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t. \u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  \u273 ang y\'ean l\u7863 ng n\u7857 m tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, c\u7853 u n\'e2ng b\'ecnh s\u7913 , c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7891 i l\'e2u, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi x\'e1c nh\u7853 n b\'ecnh s\u7913  v\u7851 n nguy\'ean v\u7865 n kh\'f4ng b\u7883  t\u7893 n h\u7841 i g\'ec m\u7899 i t\u7915  t\u7915  th\u7903  ra m\u7897 t h\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i thu d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c c\'f9ng nhau quay v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7901 ng\cb1 \
\cb3 Con \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7901 ng t\u7889 i m\u7883 t l\'fac \u273 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c g\'ec \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, l\'fac n\'e0y trong m\u7855 t T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ch\u7907 t tr\u7903  n\'ean \u273 \u7847 y qu\u7927  kh\'ed, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i x\'edch l\u7841 i g\u7847 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , sao c\u7853 u nh\u7853 n ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y th\u7913  \u273 \'f3... c\'f2n v\u7869  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'f9 n\'e0y n\u7919 a?" H\u7855 n gi\u417  tay tr\'e1i l\'ean h\u7887 i. S\u7919 a t\u7855 m \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4 l\u7841 i tr\'ean da nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m lau \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7843  nh\'e0 cha t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u theo nghi\u7879 p Thi\'ean s\u432 , cho n\'ean t\'f4i \'edt nhi\u7873 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nghe xong r\u7845 t t\'f2 m\'f2, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c gan c\u361 ng l\u7899 n h\u417 n, r\u7845 t mu\u7889 n b\'e1m l\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7887 i m\u7845 y v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  li\'ean quan, nh\u432 ng th\u7845 y b\u7841 n m\'ecnh b\u7897  d\'e1ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n n\'f3i th\'eam c\u361 ng li\u7873 n th\'f4i. H\u7855 n bi\u7871 t cha Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n c\'f3 l\u7895 i v\u7899 i hai m\u7865  con c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i con trai ru\u7897 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau t\'ecnh c\u7843 m, cho n\'ean c\'f3 l\u7869  Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\'edch cha m\'ecnh, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\'edch "Tr\'ec gia" kia, kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n c\u361 ng l\'e0 hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng h\u7855 n v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  n\u7893 i hi\u7871 u k\'ec, b\'e8n s\u7917 a mi\u7879 ng h\u7887 i: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7853 u di\u7879 t tr\u7915  th\u7913  kia r\u7891 i \'e0? Hay l\'e0 \u273 u\u7893 i \u273 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7901  l\'ean b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i. \u272 \'e2y l\'e0 b\'f9a h\u7897  m\u7879 nh c\u7911 a t\'f4i, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i l\'e0 n\'f3 \u273 \'e3 c\u7913 u t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m th\u7913  kia b\u7855 t l\u7845 y ch\'e2n c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 tho\'e1ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y t\u7915  trong b\'ecnh s\u7913  r\u417 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t tr\'e0n ra m\u7897 t l\'e0n kh\'f3i \u273 en, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c m\u7845 t \u273 i \'fd th\u7913 c, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7885 i c\u7853 u m\u7899 i t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i. M\'e0 sau khi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, th\u7913  kia \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, b\'ecnh s\u7913  l\u7841 i nguy\'ean v\u7865 n tr\'ean c\u7893 . Cho n\'ean nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 b\'ean trong b\'ecnh s\u7913  c\'f3 C\'e0n Kh\'f4n, c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng c\u7853 u \u7903  th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c m\u7845 u ch\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thu\uc0\u7853 t ph\'e1p Tr\'ec gia tu\'e2n theo Thi\'ean \u273 \u7841 o, Di\u7879 p gia l\u7841 i truy\u7873 n th\u7915 a Qu\u7927  \u273 \u7841 o, tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 Thi\'ean S\u432  th\u7871  gia nh\u432 ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 i theo h\u7879  \u273 \u7841 o ph\'e1p kh\'e1c nhau, Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\u7871 t ki\u7871 n th\u7913 c tu vi c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean k\'e9m xa ng\u432 \u7901 i kia. To\'e0n th\'e2n b\'ecnh s\u7913  k\'edn m\'edt, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  l\u7895  xuy\'ean s\u7907 i d\'e2y \u273 eo ph\'eda tr\'ean th\'ec t\'ecm kh\'f4ng ra khe h\u7903  th\u7913  hai, cho n\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng hi v\u7885 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 u huy\u7873 n c\u417  b\'ean trong b\'ecnh s\u7913  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 b\u7857 ng n\u259 ng l\u7921 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh hay l\'e0 nh\u7901  v\'e0o b\'f9a h\u7897  m\u7879 nh m\'e0 ti\'eau di\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  kia, sau khi bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7847 ng xu\u7845 t th\'e2n c\u7911 a b\u7841 n m\'ecnh li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7847 m th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t m\u7897 t v\'e0i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng d\'f9ng c\'e1ch b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 c\'e1ch nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m, b\'e2y gi\u7901  Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i th\'e0nh c\'f4ng gi\'fap \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i ma t\'e0 qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y c\'f4, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\'e0ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7841 n m\'ecnh qu\u7843  th\u7921 c n\u259 ng l\u7921 c phi ph\'e0m.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y h\u7855 n c\u361 ng l\'e0 v\'ec c\u7847 u gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  m\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'e0o ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\u7845 y ra t\u7915  trong c\u7863 p c\'f4ng v\u259 n m\u7897 t x\u7845 p \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p v\'e0 h\u7891  s\u417  v\u7909  \'e1n, ch\u7881  v\'e0o trong \u273 \'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7845 m \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p ba ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , c\u7853 u xem c\'e1i n\'e0y \u273 i, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 gia \u273 \'ecnh ba ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 Chu Huy \u7903  th\u7883  tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y, huy\u7879 n B\'ecnh C\u7889 c, th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7889 n l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m m\u7899 i l\'e1i m\u7897 t xe c\u417  gi\u7899 i ba b\'e1nh r\u7901 i th\u7883  tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y \u273 \u7871 n th\u7883  tr\u7845 n Thanh Nghi\'eau c\'e1ch \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng xa th\u259 m h\u7885  h\'e0ng, nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7871 n nay \u273 \'e3 qua m\u7897 t th\'e1ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tin t\u7913 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t v\'e0o kh\'f4ng kh\'ed v\u7853 y, b\u7845 t k\u7875  l\'e0 tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y hay l\'e0 tr\u7845 n Thanh Nghi\'eau c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tung t\'edch c\u7911 a h\u7885 . Ven \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7845 t k\u7923  manh m\u7889 i r\'f5 r\'e0ng n\'e0o."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean \u273 \'e2y v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n k\'ec l\u7841  nh\u7845 t." T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m d\u7915 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\'ecn b\u7841 n m\'ecnh n\'f3i, "Hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t huy\u7879 n B\'ecnh C\u7889 c \u273 ang \u273 i\u7873 u tra tung t\'edch gia \u273 \'ecnh n\'e0y quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh v\'e0o c\'f9ng th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m nh\'e0 Chu Huy \u273 \'e3 xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t t\u7915  Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y, \u273 i xe m\'e1y qua con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng nh\'e0 kia \u273 \'e3 \u273 i, \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh t\'ecm ki\u7871 m manh m\u7889 i. Sau \u273 \'f3... hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t."\cb1 \
