\cf2 \cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e3 g\u7847 n t\'e1m gi\u7901  r\u7891 i, sao l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n v\'e0o l\'fac n\'e0y? \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean \u273 \'e2u?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7871 c T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 ang l\u7845 y \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p v\'e0 h\u7891  s\u417  ra.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "H\'f4m nay Quy\'ean Quy\'ean tr\uc0\u7921 c ca \u273 \'eam, t\'f4i v\u7915 a \u273 \u432 a c\'f4 \u7845 y qua \u273 \'f3, ti\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  c\u7853 u. L\'e1t n\u7919 a t\'f4i v\u7873  nh\'e0 ng\u7911 , s\'e1ng mai \u273 i \u273 \'f3n c\'f4 \u7845 y v\u7873  r\u7891 i \u273 i l\'e0m." T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m n\'f3i, "V\u7909  \'e1n n\'e0y v\u7915 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e1o cho th\'e0nh ph\u7889 , s\u432  ph\u7909  t\'f4i giao l\'ean \u273 \u7847 u t\'f4i \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i t\'ecm hi\u7875 u tr\u432 \u7899 c xem c\'f3 manh m\u7889 i g\'ec kh\'f4ng, t\'f4i nghi\'ean c\u7913 u c\u7843  bu\u7893 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t t\'e0 m\'f4n, cho n\'ean mu\u7889 n mang qua cho c\u7853 u xem th\u7917 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean "Ch\uc0\u7853 c" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, b\u7887  \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p tr\'ean tay xu\u7889 ng, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "T\'f4i \u273 \'e2u ph\u7843 i chuy\'ean gia, sao t\'f4i hi\u7875 u m\u7845 y c\'e1i n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7841 o thu\u7853 t sao?" T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m h\u7855 c h\u7855 c c\u432 \u7901 i: "C\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng c\'f3 khi\'eam t\u7889 n n\u7919 a", ch\u7881  ch\u7881  \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p n\'f3i, "T\'f4i th\u7845 y tr\'ean phim c\'f3 lo\u7841 i thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p n\'e0y m\'e0, nh\'ecn \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7847 m v\u7853 t d\u7909 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng d\'f9ng l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'ednh ra tung t\'edch. T\'f4i ngh\u297 ... bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y h\u7855 n c\u361 ng x\u7845 u h\u7893  m\'e0 g\'e3i g\'e3i t\'f3c, b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \'fd t\u432 \u7903 ng n\'e0y kh\'f4ng kh\u7843  thi. B\u7841 n m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c \u273 u\u7893 i nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia, nh\u432 ng ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c lo\u7841 i thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh n\'f3i: "C\'e1i t\'f4i d\'f9ng \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 \u7841 o thu\u7853 t, nh\u432 ng t\'f4i bi\u7871 t c\'f3 thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 , c\u361 ng c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 t s\u7917  d\u7909 ng, \u273 \'e1ng ti\u7871 c l\'e0 t\'f4i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t." Lo\u7841 i thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'ecm \u273 \u7891  v\u7853 t n\'e0y kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 cao th\'e2m, Tr\'ec gia c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\'ednh l\'e0 "ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec gia ".\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i v\u7915 a \u273 \u7885 c mi\'eau t\u7843  t\'ecnh ti\u7871 t v\u7909  \'e1n, l\'f4ng m\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i cau l\u7841 i: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng, v\u7909  n\'e0y g\u7845 p l\u7855 m sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "G\uc0\u7845 p," T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, "D\'f9 sao c\u361 ng li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n t\'ednh m\u7841 ng n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i. Hi\'ea\u803 n ta\u803 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7889 ng ch\u7871 t ra sao, n\u7871 u nh\u432  \u273 ang g\u7863 p t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng nguy hi\u7875 m, c\'e0ng s\u7899 m t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7885 n h\u7885  th\'ec hi v\u7885 ng c\u7913 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7869  c\'e0ng l\u7899 n h\u417 n. H\u417 n n\u7919 a \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 v\u7909  \'e1n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean mang t\'ednh chuy\'ean m\'f4n m\'e0 s\u432  ph\u7909  giao cho t\'f4i, t\'f4i mu\u7889 n gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t xong r\u7891 i cho \'f4ng \u7845 y xem."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Tr\'ean n\'e0y vi\u7871 t, nh\'e0 Chu Huy m\u7903  ti\u7879 m t\u7841 p h\'f3a nh\u7887  \u7903  Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y, v\'ec kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c tr\u7877  d\u7903 , b\u7843 y gi\u7901  t\u7889 i ng\'e0y m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m th\'e1ng Gi\'eang sau khi \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a h\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 l\'e1i xe c\u417  gi\u7899 i ba b\'e1nh tr\u7903  v\u7873  th\u7883  tr\u7845 n Thanh Nghi\'eau, m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch l\'e0 quay v\u7873  th\u259 m nh\'e0 m\u7865  v\u7907  m\'ecnh L\u432 u Thanh Ph\u432 \u7907 ng, qua m\u432 \u7901 i s\'e1u th\'e1ng gi\'eang l\u7841 i v\'f2ng v\'e0o huy\u7879 n l\u7845 y h\'e0ng sau \u273 \'f3 quay v\u7873  l\u7841 i Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y. V\u7873  \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y l\u7901 i khai c\u7911 a h\'e0ng x\'f3m nh\'e0 Chu Huy v\'e0 nh\'e0 m\u7865  \u273 \u7867  L\u432 u Thanh Ph\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7891 ng nh\u7845 t, n\u7871 u m\u7885 i vi\u7879 c su\'f4n s\u7867  th\'ec ba ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 Chu Huy ch\u7915 ng m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  t\u7889 i s\u7869  \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 m\u7865  \u273 \u7867  L\u432 u Thanh Ph\u432 \u7907 ng, nh\u432 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, anh trai L\u432 u Thanh Ph\u432 \u7907 ng kh\'f4ng li\'ean l\u7841 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7899 i h\u7885 , \u273 \u7907 i qua m\u7897 t ng\'e0y m\u432 \u7901 i s\'e1u th\'e1ng Gi\'eang, \u273 \u7871 n s\'e1ng s\u7899 m ng\'e0y m\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 y ch\u7841 y \u273 i Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y h\u7887 i th\u259 m h\'e0ng x\'f3m m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t c\u7843  nh\'e0 h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 \u273 i t\u7915  l\'e2u r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Cho n\'ean hai vi\'ean c\uc0\u7843 nh s\'e1t huy\u7879 n B\'ecnh C\u7889 c ph\'e1n \u273 o\'e1n b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\u7845 t t\'edch tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng t\u7915  tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y \u273 \u7871 n tr\u7845 n Thanh Nghi\'eau, nh\u432 ng ban ng\'e0y khi t\'ecm manh m\u7889 i \u7903  ven \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4ng tin g\'ec c\'f3 gi\'e1 tr\u7883 , sau m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n r\u7855 c r\u7889 i h\u7885  quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u tra x\'e9t l\u7841 i \u7903  ven \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng v\'e0o b\u7843 y gi\u7901  t\u7889 i, hy v\u7885 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t \'edt manh m\u7889 i ban ng\'e0y d\u7877  b\u7887  qua ho\u7863 c \u273 \'e3 xem nh\u7865 ... K\u7871 t qu\u7843  l\'e0 hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng m\u7845 t t\'edch."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 l\u7869  th\u7901 i gian xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t n\'e0y qu\u7843  th\u7921 c c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng sai." T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m bu\u7891 n b\u7921 c c\'e0o c\'e0o t\'f3c, "M\u7845 y th\u7913  n\'e0y t\'f4i c\u361 ng hi\u7875 u. Ng\'e0y mai Quy\'ean Quy\'ean ngh\u7881  ca s\'e1ng, t\'f4i \u273 ang \u273 \u7883 nh ng\'e0y mai \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  b\'e1o v\u7899 i s\u432  ph\u7909  r\u7891 i \u273 i tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y nh\'ecn th\u7917  xem c\'f3 manh m\u7889 i g\'ec kh\'f4ng, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\'ec \u273 \u7907 i t\u7899 i b\u7843 y gi\u7901  t\u7889 i s\u7869  qua con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i tr\u7845 n Thanh Nghi\'eau kia."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n th\u7847 m m\u7855 ng m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "T\'f4i v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng tin th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 ma \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i\u7873 m t\u297 nh nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "Th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 ma \u273 \u7845 y, c\u7853 u c\'f2n t\u7915 ng b\'e1i ki\u7871 n r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, xanh c\u7843  m\u7863 t, o\'e1n h\u7853 n n\'f3i: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 !"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907 . Hai ng\'e0y n\'e0y \u273 \'fang d\u7883 p t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, ch\u7901  t\'f4i n\'f3i v\u7899 i \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, ng\'e0y mai \u273 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7901 i n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean m\u7915 ng r\u7905 , h\u7865 n ng\'e0y mai sau khi r\u7901 i \u273 \u417 n v\u7883  s\u7869  t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e0 c\'f3 b\'e1nh s\uc0\u7911 i c\u7843 o \u273 \'f4ng l\u7841 nh v\'e0 l\u7841 p x\u432 \u7903 ng hun kh\'f3i, \u273 \u7891  h\u7897 p \u273 \u7891  \u259 n nhanh c\'e1c lo\u7841 i, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i ch\u7871  bi\u7871 n s\u417  qua l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u259 n, \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean ng\'e0y mai l\'fac \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881  c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  qua \u273 \u432 a c\u417 m cho \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i. \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c t\u7887  v\u7867  c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh v\u7851 n r\u7845 t kh\u7887 e, t\u7921  m\'ecnh x\u7917  l\'fd sinh ho\u7841 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec, cho d\'f9 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u432 \u7901 i ng\'e0y n\u7917 a th\'e1ng kh\'f4ng tr\u7903  l\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m sau m\uc0\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  h\u417 n T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u, m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901  tr\u432 a th\'ec \u273 \u7871 n tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y. M\u7897 t vi\'ean c\u7843 nh s\'e1t h\u7885  L\'fd ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3n b\u7885 n h\u7885 , d\u7851 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7879 m t\u7841 p h\'f3a nh\'e0 Chu Huy, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\u361 ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i h\'e0ng x\'f3m xung quanh, tin t\u7913 c l\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec b\u7845 t \u273 \u7891 ng v\u7899 i h\u7891  s\u417  v\u7909  \'e1n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  trong tr\u7845 n \u273 i h\u7887 i th\u259 m m\u7897 t bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a, c\u361 ng \u273 i xe m\'e1y m\u7897 t v\'f2ng gi\u7919 a hai th\u7883  tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y Thanh Nghi\'eau, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'eam manh m\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi tr\uc0\u7903  l\u7841 i Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y th\'ec \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 n\u259 m gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i: "\u258 n c\u417 m tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i, c\u417 m n\u432 \u7899 c xong xu\'f4i \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n b\u7843 y gi\u7901  ch\'fang ta s\u7869  \u273 i xem th\u7917 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Vi\'ean c\uc0\u7843 nh s\'e1t h\u7885  L\'fd nghe v\u7853 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng h\u417 i s\u7907  h\'e3i, ng\u432 \u7907 ng ng\u7853 p n\'f3i v\u7899 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i: "T\'f4i \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng s\u7855 p \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  tan l\'e0m, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f9ng hai v\u7883  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, hai v\u7883  c\'f3 \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nheo m\u7855 t \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 h\u7855 n: "Con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7871 n t\u7889 i s\u7869  c\'f3 g\'ec b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 nh s\'e1t h\u7885  L\'fd b\u7845 t an xoa xoa tay, do d\u7921  n\'f3i: "C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, ch\u7881  l\'e0 t\u7915  th\'e1ng Gi\'eang \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  m\u7845 t n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i, c\'f2n c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0 \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p c\u7911 a t\'f4i. M\u7863 c d\'f9 n\'f3i ch\'fang t\'f4i kh\'f4ng tin c\'e1i n\'e0y, nh\u432 ng trong l\'f2ng \'edt nhi\u7873 u c\u361 ng e ng\u7841 i, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i kh\'f4ng ai d\'e1m \u273 i con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n: "V\u7853 y tr\u432 \u7899 c kia kh\'f4ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y sao? Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u273 i t\u7915  Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y \u273 \u7871 n Thanh Nghi\'eau v\'e0o bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i th\'ec sao? H\u7885  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng m\u7845 t t\'edch sao? L\u7841 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'e0 Chu Huy v\'e0 hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t t\'ecm tung t\'edch b\u7885 n h\u7885  bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Vi\'ean c\uc0\u7843 nh s\'e1t \u273 \'e1p: "Con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f3 bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u ch\'fang ta \u273 \'e3 \u273 i qua, nh\u7883  v\u7883  c\u361 ng th\u7845 y r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y, r\u7845 t h\u7865 p, \u273 i xe h\u417 i kh\'f4ng v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. \u272 \u7841 i l\u7897  t\u7915  Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y \u273 \u7871 n Thanh Nghi\'eau kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\'e0 Chu Huy v\'ec mu\u7889 n \u273 i nhanh n\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'f2n xuy\'ean n\'fai, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f3 r\u7845 t \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i. Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n s\u7921  t\'ecnh t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 , theo l\u7901 i h\'e0ng x\'f3m n\'f3i th\'ec tr\u432 \u7899 c kia nh\'e0 Chu Huy c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng \u273 i con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y, c\'f2n d\u7851 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i qua, t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7899 i gi\u7901  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, b\u7843 o vi\'ean c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia v\u7873 , ch\u7881  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c m\u432 \u7907 n hai chi\u7871 c xe m\'e1y b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i l\'fac chi\u7873 u, n\'f3i l\'e0 sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  s\u7869  tr\u7843  l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n b\u7843 y gi\u7901  t\u7889 i th\'ec b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 i d\u7885 c theo con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'f2n trong n\'fai. L\'fac n\'e0y ch\u7881  m\u7899 i gi\u7919 a th\'e1ng ba, ph\u432 \u417 ng b\u7855 c r\'e9t th\'e1ng ba, th\u7901 i ti\u7871 t kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u7845 m \'e1p, sau khi m\u259 \u803 t tr\u417 \u768 i xu\u244 \u769 ng n\'fai l\u7841 i c\'e0ng th\'eam l\u7841 nh. C\'f2n ch\u432 a t\u7899 i xu\'e2n ph\'e2n, tr\u7901 i t\u7889 i r\u7845 t nhanh, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 t\u7889 i m\u7883 t ho\'e0n to\'e0n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7921 a v\'e0o \u273 \'e8n xe m\'e1y soi \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i kh\'f4ng nhanh, m\u7897 t b\'ean l\'e1i m\u7897 t b\'ean chi\u7871 u \u273 \'e8n pin quan s\'e1t t\'ecnh h\'ecnh hai b\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nh\'ecn b\'ean tr\'e1i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn b\'ean ph\u7843 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u417 n hai gi\u7901  ph\'eda sau n\'fai d\u7847 n n\u7893 i l\'ean s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9, t\u7847 m nh\'ecn c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5, Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'e9o k\'e9o \'e1o kho\'e1c, l\u7841 nh run c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i, quay \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng, tr\u7901 i l\u7841 nh qu\'e1 r\u7891 i, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y r\'f5 l\u7855 m, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ch\'fang ta tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 i, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n tr\u7845 n Thanh Nghi\'eau ngh\u7881 , ng\'e0y mai l\u7841 i t\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n c\u7853 u m\'e0 nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'ean tr\'e1i, sau m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u m\u7899 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng, c\u7847 m \u273 \'e8n pin chi\u7871 u v\u7873  m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , c\u7853 u xem b\'ean kia c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn theo \'e1nh \uc0\u273 \'e8n. Trong n\'fai t\u7889 i \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 h\'ecnh b\'f3ng lay \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a c\'e2y c\u7889 i r\u7853 m r\u7841 p v\'e0 th\u7843 m th\u7921 c v\u7853 t m\u7885 c h\u7895 n t\u7841 p, d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7897 t g\u7889 c c\'e2y c\'f3 m\u7897 t con m\u432 \u417 ng nh\u7887 , nh\u7901  \'e1nh s\'e1ng c\u7911 a \u273 \'e8n pin c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7913  m\'e0u \u273 o\u777 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn h\uc0\u417 i quen m\u7855 t. H\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 m\u7897 t g\'f3c chi\u7871 c xe c\u417  gi\u7899 i trong \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p nh\'e0 Chu Huy.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, tr\u7903  m\'ecnh xu\u7889 ng xe, ch\u7889 ng xe m\'e1y tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 i qua ch\u7895  kia. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng \u273 i theo qua \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kho\uc0\u7843 ng c\'e1ch r\u7845 t g\u7847 n, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 ch\u7855 n t\u7847 m nh\'ecn l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\'f3 th\u7875  r\u7845 t nh\u7853 n ra \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 chi\u7871 c xe c\u7911 a nh\'e0 Chu Huy. C\u7843  th\'e2n xe \u273 \u7873 u l\u7853 t trong m\u432 \u417 ng, nh\u432 ng xung quanh r\u7845 t s\u7841 ch s\u7869 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\'e0ng h\'f3a r\u417 i v\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng ra ch\u7909 p \u7843 nh xe, v\u7915 a ch\u7909 p v\u7915 a ph\'e2n t\'edch n\'f3i: "H\u7859 n l\'e0 tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i xe x\u7843 y ra v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  b\u7883  l\u7853 t v\'e0o m\u432 \u417 ng, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7867  c\'f3 th\u432 \u417 ng vong. Nh\'e0 Chu Huy d\u7921  \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 i th\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n r\u7891 i sau \u273 \'f3 nh\u7853 p h\'e0ng, h\'e0nh l\'fd mang theo kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m, nh\'ecn qua c\'f3 v\u7867  b\u7883  mang \u273 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng k\'e9o xe ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, cho n\'ean kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i \u273 i t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , nh\u432 ng t\u7915  \u273 \'e2y \u273 i b\u7897  v\u7873  tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y ph\u7843 i m\u7845 t ba b\u7889 n ti\u7871 ng, \u273 \u7871 n tr\u7845 n Thanh Nghi\'eau c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i m\u7897 t hai ti\u7871 ng. V\u7853 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i tr\u7845 n Thanh Nghi\'eau r\u7891 i?" T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ch\u7909 p xong c\u7845 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, v\u7915 a b\'e0n b\u7841 c v\u7915 a ph\'e2n t\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \'fang." Tr\'ec Di\'ean qu\u417  qu\u417  \u273 \'e8n pin, \'fd b\u7843 o nh\'ecn xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n, "Nh\'ecn \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y, c\'f3 d\u7845 u v\u7871 t c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i qua, c\'f2n c\'f3 v\u7871 t b\'e1nh xe l\u259 n qua n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nh\'ecn t\u7915  d\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n h\u432 \u7899 ng ra xa, n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'e1nh r\u7869 , l\'e0 m\u7897 t con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7887  ch\u7881  \u273 \u7911  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn k\u7929  s\u7869  r\u7845 t kh\'f3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n. Ban ng\'e0y b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chi\u7871 c xe n\'e0y, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\'f2n c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n l\u7841 i ng\u7891 i x\u7893 m xu\u7889 ng xem x\'e9t t\u432 \u7901 ng t\u7853 n b\'e3i c\u7887  c\'f3 d\u7845 u v\u7871 t: "Kh\'f4ng sai, l\'e0 v\u7871 t b\'e1nh xe, h\u7859 n l\'e0 l\u432 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng l\'e2u tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y. Hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra chi\u7871 c xe, sau \u273 \'f3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y, cho n\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 u\u7893 i theo d\u7885 c con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y k\u7923  qu\u7863 c, ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7889 i \u273 en v\u7855 ng l\u7863 ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7845 t k\u7923  d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u n\'e0o c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i hay c\'f3 th\'f4n x\'f3m, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\'f3i l\u7917 a. Hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t v\'ec truy t\'ecm tung t\'edch nh\'e0 Chu Huy m\'e0 \u273 i theo con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y th\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u432 ng l\'fac \u7845 y nh\'e0 Chu Huy \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y v\'ec sao l\u7841 i ch\u7885 n \u273 i theo con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng v\u7855 ng v\u7867  khu\u7845 t n\u7867 o, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t cu\u7889 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  th\'f4ng t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2u n\'e0y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 xu\'f4i theo con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng quen thu\u7897 c cu\u777 a bo\u803 n h\u7885  quay v\u7873  Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y ho\u7863 c \u273 i Thanh Nghi\'eau?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i l\u7841 nh, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i r\'f9ng m\'ecnh m\u7897 t c\'e1i, l\u7841 i k\'e9o ch\u7863 t qu\u7847 n \'e1o, c\'e0ng mu\u7889 n quay v\u7873  h\u417 n. C\u7853 u l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng ra nh\'ecn, \u273 \'e3 ch\'edn r\u432 \u7905 i t\u7889 i, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Internet.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay sang T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng, b\'e2y gi\u7901  mu\u7897 n r\u7891 i, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'fai kh\'f4ng d\u7877  \u273 i \u273 \'e2u, tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 i nhanh c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901 . Nh\u7899  k\u7929  v\u7883  tr\'ed n\'e0y, \u273 \'e1nh d\u7845 u l\u7841 i, ng\'e0y mai ch\'fang ta l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u361 ng l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ra xem, kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng n\'f3i: "Ch\'fang ta th\u7915 a d\u7883 p hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 i xem lu\'f4n \u273 i, ng\u7897  nh\u7905  ng\'e0y mai ban ng\'e0y l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra manh m\u7889 i n\u7919 a. B\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 9h30, ch\'fang ta \u273 i theo con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n 9h45, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \u7847 u m\u7889 i g\'ec th\'ec tr\u7903  v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
