\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 i ngay m\'e0 quay tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ch\u7895  xe m\'e1y, l\u7845 y b\u7853 t l\u7917 a \u273 \u7889 t hai t\u7845 m ph\'f9. \u272 \'e2y g\u7885 i l\'e0 ph\'f9 d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\'e0 Chu Huy v\'e0 hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia sau khi \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\u7903  v\u7873 , c\u7853 u nghi ng\u7901  tr\'ean con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  c\'f3 c\u7893  qu\'e1i, c\'f3 ph\'f9 d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y s\u7869  kh\'f4ng s\u7907  g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i ma d\u7921 ng t\u432 \u7901 ng hay th\u7913  g\'ec kh\'e1c, c\'f3 th\u7875  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i l\'e1i xe \u273 i d\u7885 c theo con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7915 a \u273 i v\u7915 a ch\'fa \'fd t\'ecnh h\'ecnh hai b\'ean. V\u7871 t b\'e1nh xe tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t d\u7847 n tr\u7903  n\'ean kh\'f4ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng, con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng do ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i gi\u7851 m ra t\u7841 o th\'e0nh c\u361 ng d\u7847 n bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'e0 m\u7897 t v\'f9ng n\'fai r\u7915 ng r\u7853 m r\u7841 p. \u272 ang l\'fac hai ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean \u273 i theo h\u432 \u7899 ng n\'e0o, do d\u7921  m\'e0 quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh quay v\u7873 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7907 t th\u7845 y ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n th\u7845 p tho\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\u7915 ng xe, b\'f2 l\'ean t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 l\u7899 n b\'ean c\u7841 nh nh\'ecn ra xa\'97\'97 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\u7897 t ng\u7885 n \u273 \'e8n m\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t khu, nh\'ecn qua gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t th\'f4n nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\'f2 xu\uc0\u7889 ng t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1, \'fd b\u7843 o T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m tr\'e8o l\'ean nh\'ecn, \u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng, c\u7853 u xem b\'ean kia c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\'e1i th\'f4n kh\'f4ng? C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i quanh \u273 \'e2y c\'f3 th\'f4n tr\u7845 n n\'e0o kh\'e1c ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m l\'ean c\u7845 p ba Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo m\u7865  v\'e0o th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, sau \u273 \'f3 v\u7851 n lu\'f4n s\u7889 ng trong th\'e0nh ph\u7889 , ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  l\'fac \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881  th\'ec r\u7845 t \'edt khi \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1c th\u7883  tr\u7845 n xung quanh. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 t\'ean v\'e0 v\u7883  tr\'ed m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t huy\u7879 n thu\u7897 c th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, nh\u432 ng d\u432 \u7899 i huy\u7879 n c\'f2n c\'f3 th\'f4n tr\u7845 n n\'e0o th\'ec ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng r\'f5, c\u361 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec chuy\u7879 n l\u7847 n n\'e0y m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t d\u432 \u7899 i huy\u7879 n B\'ecnh C\u7889 c c\'f3 hai th\u7883  tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y v\'e0 Thanh Nghi\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m t\u7915  tr\'ean t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 nh\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'fang l\'e0 c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\'f4n. L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 tra x\'e9t r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n b\u7843 n \u273 \u7891  xung quanh Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y v\'e0 Thanh Nghi\'eau, kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd l\'e0 c\'f3 th\'f4n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, nh\u432 ng ng\u7885 n n\'fai n\'e0y l\'e0 ranh gi\u7899 i gi\u7919 a huy\u7879 n B\'ecnh C\u7889 c v\'e0 huy\u7879 n Huy L\'e2m, xa h\u417 n b\'ean kia \u273 i c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'e0 huy\u7879 n Huy L\'e2m r\u7891 i, n\'ean t\'f4i kh\'f4ng \u273 \'ea\u777  \'fd \u273 \u234 \u769 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Quanh Ph\uc0\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y v\'e0 Thanh Nghi\'eau c\'f3 g\u7847 n ba m\u432 \u417 i th\'f4n, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng kh\u7843 o s\'e1t th\u7921 c \u273 \u7883 a s\u7869  r\u7845 t d\u7877  b\u7887  qua th\'f4n l\'e0ng v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng thu\u7897 c ph\u7841 m vi huy\u7879 n B\'ecnh C\u7889 c n\'e0y, d\'f9 sao n\'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\u7857 m tr\'ean tuy\u7871 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng qua l\u7841 i gi\u7919 a hai tr\u7845 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, tr\u432 ng c\u7847 u \'fd ki\u7871 n: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , b\'e2y gi\u7901  ch\'fang ta tr\u7903  v\u7873  t\'ecm hi\u7875 u th\'f4n kia, ng\'e0y mai ban ng\'e0y l\u7841 i quay l\u7841 i hay l\'e0 qua \u273 \'f3 xem lu\'f4n?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Hi\uc0\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 21h45, nh\'ecn t\u7915  \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7875  \u273 o\'e1n, th\'f4n kia c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 nh\u7887 , c\'f3 l\u7869  \'edt nh\u7845 t c\u361 ng h\u417 n m\u432 \u7901 i h\u7897  gia \u273 \'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn ra T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ch\u7881  e l\'e0 v\u7851 n mu\u7889 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i, th\'f4n nh\u7887  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\u7883  xem nh\u7865  n\'e0y r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  cung c\u7845 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\'fat manh m\u7889 i v\u7873  n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 t t\'edch. C\u7853 u t\'ednh s\u417  qua th\u7901 i gian v\'e0 qu\'e3ng \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873 , \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883 : "Hay l\'e0 ch\'fang ta c\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i, v\'e0o th\'f4n r\u7891 i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ban \uc0\u273 \'eam tr\'ean n\'fai r\u7845 t l\u7841 nh, c\u7853 u m\u7863 c \'edt \u273 \u7891 , \u273 i xe m\'e1y trong gi\'f3 c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng run c\u7847 m c\u7853 p, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u th\u7921 c s\u7921  \u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\u259 n ph\'f2ng \u7845 m \'e1p gi\'fap c\u7853 u l\'e0m \u7845 m c\u417  th\u7875 , t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  chui v\'e0o ch\u259 n l\'e0m m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c. Tr\u7903  v\u7873  Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y hay Thanh Nghi\'eau \u273 \u7873 u ph\u7843 i ch\u7915 ng m\u7897 t gi\u7901 , nh\u432 ng nh\'ecn kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch t\u7915  \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u7871 n th\'f4n kia th\'ec ch\u7881  t\u7847 m m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n c\u7893 ng th\'f4n th\'ec d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, t\'f4i \u273 i v\'e0o tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'ecm hi\u7875 u t\'ecnh h\'ecnh, n\u7871 u th\u7845 y qua m\u7897 t ph\'fat m\'e0 t\'f4i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ra th\'ec \u273 \u7915 ng do d\u7921  m\'e0 ch\u7841 y nhanh \u273 i, tr\u7903  l\u7841 i tr\u7845 n \u273 \'f3n vi\u7879 n binh." L\'fac n\'e0y h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i s\u7907  y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i c\'e1c loa\u803 i m\'e0 l\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng s\u7869  x\u7843 y ra t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng nh\u432  trong phim, th\'f4n l\'e0ng \u7849 n trong n\'fai k\u7923  th\u7853 t \u273 ang ch\u7913 a ch\u7845 p ph\u7847 n t\u7917  t\u7897 i ph\u7841 m, nh\'e0 Chu Huy v\'e0 hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra ch\u7895  \u7849 n n\'e1u c\u7911 a b\u7885 n ch\'fang m\'e0 b\u7883  b\u7855 t c\'f3c, th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 b\u7883  gi\u7871 t h\u7841 i. Ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n kh\u7843  n\u259 ng \u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n c\'e0ng \u273 \u7913 ng ng\u7891 i kh\'f4ng y\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, tr\u7903  m\'ecnh l\'ean xe m\'e1y, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda th\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean sau khi ch\u7841 y ch\u7915 ng m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng sau n\'fai d\u7847 n r\u7897 ng ra, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0o th\'f4n tr\u7903  n\'ean r\'f5 r\'e0ng. T\'edn hi\u7879 u Internet tuy r\u7857 ng v\u7851 n ch\u7853 p ch\u7901 n nh\u432  c\u361  nh\u432 ng \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\'f3ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u t\u244 \u769 c \u273 \'f4\u803  \u273 \u432 \u417 \u768 ng truy\u234 \u768 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng ch\u7853 m, l\'fac \u273 \u7913 t l\'fac n\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\'f3ng v\'e0 Internet l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta y\'ean t\'e2m h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u, m\u7903  b\u7843 n \u273 \u7891  ra, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i tra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u417 i n\'e0y g\u7885 i l\'e0 th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7851 n ch\u432 a y\'ean t\'e2m, ra ngo\'e0i th\'f4n t\'ecm n\u417 i c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u t\u7889 t h\u417 n g\u7885 i cho s\u432  ph\u7909 , b\'e1o c\'e1o manh m\u7889 i li\'ean quan t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0 v\u7883  tr\'ed hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, c\u361 ng nh\u7901  s\u432  ph\u7909  h\u7895  tr\u7907  t\'ecm hi\u7875 u t\'ecnh h\'ecnh trong th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 K\uc0\u7871 t qu\u7843  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng tra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t th\'f4n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, duy nh\u7845 t m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m h\u417 i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t l\'e0 \u273 \u7841 i b\u7897  ph\u7853 n th\'f4n d\'e2n \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 t\u7915  ph\'eda nam d\u7901 i t\u7899 i nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1p \'e1n n\'e0y \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i b\'e1o c\'e1o h\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh xong, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean y\'ean t\'e2m h\u417 n r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p mang theo Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng ti\u7871 n v\'e0o th\'f4n. \u272 \u7847 u th\'f4n c\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'e0 b\'e1n t\u7841 p h\'f3a v\u7851 n s\'e1ng \u273 \'e8n, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m d\u7915 ng xe v\'e0o mua m\u7897 t h\u7897 p thu\u7889 c l\'e1 v\'e0 hai chai n\u432 \u7899 c, thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n th\u259 m d\'f2 ch\'fat t\'ecnh h\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7911  ti\u7879 m ch\u7881  cho b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\'f3i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i v\'e0o trong kh\'f4ng xa c\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'e0 tr\u7885 , l\'e0 nh\'e0 tr\u7885  ki\'eam qu\'e1n \u259 n duy nh\u7845 t trong th\'f4n. T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh \u7903  l\u7841 i ngay ch\u7895  n\'e0y ngh\u7881  qua \u273 \'eam, ng\'e0y mai ban ng\'e0y s\u7869  \u273 i h\u7887 i th\u259 m tin t\u7913 c trong th\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c ba m\u432 \u417 i m\'e9t th\'ec th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\u7843 ng hi\u7879 u h\'ecnh ch\u7919  nh\u7853 t n\u7873 n \u273 \u7887  ch\u7919  tr\u7855 ng, d\'f9ng *T\u7889 ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7873  l\u7899 n ba ch\u7919  "Nh\'e0 tr\u7885 ". M\u7863 t ti\u7873 n kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, \'e1nh s\'e1ng l\u417 \u768  m\u417 \u768  y\u7871 u \u7899 t t\u7915  b\'f3ng \u273 \'e8n chi\u7871 u xuy\'ean qua c\u7917 a, c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y b\'ean trong c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c qu\u7847 y ki\u7875 u c\u361 , ph\'eda sau qu\u7847 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng trung ni\'ean \u273 ang ng\u7891 i.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (*T\uc0\u7889 ng th\u7875 : ki\u7875 u ch\u7919  vu\'f4ng \u273 \u7901 i T\u7889 ng)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i v\'e0o, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7899 i bu\'f4ng m\'e1y ch\u417 i game trong tay xu\u7889 ng, \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean ch\'e0o h\u7887 i: "\u7902  tr\u7885  sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean tr\uc0\u7847 n nh\'e0 treo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 \'e8n tu\'fdp, b\'f3ng \u273 \'e8n \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\'e2u kh\'f4ng thay, hai \u273 \u7847 u bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh m\'e0u \u273 en, ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a ph\u7911 i b\u7909 i d\'e0y, ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng vang \'f4ng \'f4ng, \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n kh\'f4ng m\u7845 y s\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn tr\'f2 ch\u417 i kia, m\'e0n h\'ecnh \u273 en tr\u7855 ng hi\u7875 n th\u7883  game B\u7855 n xe t\u259 ng. C\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 khi c\u7853 u t\u7847 m n\u259 m, s\'e1u tu\u7893 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'e1y ch\u417 i game n\'e0y, l\'e0 m\u7865  mua cho c\u7853 u, tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , chi\u7871 c m\'e1y \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 c\'f9ng c\u7853 u v\u432 \u7907 t qua r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian ch\'e1n n\u7843 n bu\u7891 n b\'e3. Kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i b\'e2y gi\u7901  v\u7851 n c\'f2n c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u417 i tr\'f2 n\'e0y, h\u7859 n l\'e0 \'f4ng ch\u7911  tr\u7885  ch\u417 i \u273 \u7875  gi\u7871 t th\u7901 i gian.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7885 n m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng \u273 \'f4i, thu ti\u7873 n ghi s\u7893  xong \'f4ng ch\u7911  t\u7921  m\'ecnh c\u7847 m ch\'eca kh\'f3a \u273 \u432 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean ph\'f2ng. N\u417 i \u273 \'e2y c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng v\u7851 n d\'f9ng ch\'eca kh\'f3a m\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng th\u7867  t\u7915 . Tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i ba ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m gi\u7843  v\u7901  m\'ecnh \u273 i du l\u7883 ch \u7903  v\'f9ng ph\u7909  c\u7853 n, quay v\u7873  mu\u7897 n, tr\u7901 i l\u7841 i l\u7841 nh, v\u7915 a \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u273 i ngang qua n\'ean mu\u7889 n \u7903  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam r\u7891 i mai l\u7841 i l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  n\'f3i cho b\u7885 n h\u7885  bi\u7871 t b\'e2y gi\u7901  v\u7915 a h\u7871 t n\u259 m, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ngh\u7881  ch\'e2n, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0 kh\'e1ch. Nh\'e0 tr\u7885  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nh\'e2n vi\'ean, h\u7857 ng ng\'e0y c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c qu\'e9t d\u7885 n t\'ednh ti\u7873 n \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 do h\u7855 n v\'e0 v\u7907  l\'e0m, ngo\'e0i ra trong nh\'e0 tr\u7885  c\'f2n c\'f3 con g\'e1i t\'e1m tu\u7893 i c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e0 tr\uc0\u7885  kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, t\u7893 ng c\u7897 ng c\'f3 hai l\u7847 u, l\u7847 u m\u7897 t l\'e0 qu\u7847 y ti\u7871 p kh\'e1ch, qu\'e1n \u259 n th\'ec \u259 n c\'f9ng ch\u7895  v\u7899 i gia \u273 \'ecnh \'f4ng ch\u7911 , l\u7847 u hai c\'f3 b\u7843 y, t\'e1m ph\'f2ng cho kh\'e1ch, \'f4ng ch\u7911  d\u7851 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i xem ph\'f2ng, \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i ch\'eca kh\'f3a r\u7891 i r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 t\u7889 t, b\u7889 n ph\'eda t\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7855 ng \u273 \'e3 h\u417 i \u7889  v\'e0ng, nh\'ecn k\u7929  c\'f2n c\'f3 c\'f4n tr\'f9ng ho\u7863 c v\u7871 t b\u7849 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t do th\u7913  g\'ec l\u432 u l\u7841 i. Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\'f2ng v\u7879  sinh, trong ph\'f2ng ch\u7881  b\'e0y m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c b\'e0n m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c gh\u7871  v\'e0 hai chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u361 ng may ga gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn c\'f2n t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i s\u7841 ch s\u7869 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\'f4ng m\u7845 y \u273 \u7875  \'fd v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u t\u7915  b\'e9. M\u7865  c\u7853 u tuy r\u7857 ng th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7853 u nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng nu\'f4ng chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7901 i duy nh\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 nu\'f4ng chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i kia. M\'e0 sau khi c\'f9ng m\u7865  tr\u7903  l\u7841 i nh\'e0 \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e c\u7911 a m\u7865  c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng k\'e9m, \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 qua s\'e1u m\u432 \u417 i, \u7903  nh\'e0 c\u7853 u l\u7841 i c\'e0ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng t\u7921  l\u7853 p, kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u7927  l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7889 i trong nh\'e0 m\'e0 c\'f2n ph\u7843 i ch\u259 m s\'f3c m\u7865  v\'e0 \'f4ng b\'e0. D\u432 \u7899 i ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7901 i ni\'ean thi\u7871 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  s\u7911 ng th\'e0nh th\'edch l\'e0m n\u361 ng r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  m\'e0i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh d\u7915 ng ch\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7855 t b\u7867  g\'ec, \u273 i\u7875 m duy nh\u7845 t c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng \u7893 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 nh\'e0 tr\u7885  trong kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\u7879  th\u7889 ng s\u432 \u7903 i, gian ph\'f2ng th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903 , c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \'e2m l\'e3nh, d\'f9 \u273 \'e3 \u7903  trong ph\'f2ng h\u417 n hai gi\u7901 , d\'f9ng ch\u259 n bao k\u7929  l\u7841 i nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f3 xua \u273 i h\'e0n \'fd trong c\u417  th\u7875 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i nh\'ecn, \u273 \'e3 m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t r\u432 \u7905 i \u273 \'eam, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m ng\u7911  say, ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng ng\'e1y r\u7845 t nh\u7887 . Trong ph\'f2ng t\u7889 i \u273 en, k\'e9o m\'e0n che ra kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7843 nh \u273 \'eam b\'ean ngo\'e0i, trong th\'f4n r\u7845 t y\'ean t\u297 nh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ch\'ecm v\'e0o gi\u7845 c ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng b\'f2 d\u7853 y, c\u7847 m ch\'eca kh\'f3a ph\'f2ng v\'e0 \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, kh\'f3a c\u7917 a xong \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 v\u7879  sinh. M\u7895 i gian ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m ri\'eang, \u7903  cu\u7889 i h\'e0nh lang c\'f3 m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng v\u7879  sinh chung, ngo\'e0i ra c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m nh\u7887 . H\'e0nh lang r\u7845 t t\u7889 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7885  l\u7841 i th\'eam mu\u7889 n ti\u234 \u769 t ki\'ea\u803 m \u273 i\'ea\u803 n hay kh\'f4ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \'e8n s\'e1ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i d\'f9ng \u273 i\'ea\u803 n thoa\u803 i soi \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng v\u7879  sinh trong c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  ph\'f2ng v\u7879  sinh \u273 i ra Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n pin chi\u7871 u \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng h\'e0nh lang. \'c1nh \u273 \'e8n tr\u7855 ng lo\'e1ng l\'ean m\u7897 t c\'e1i, qu\'e9t qua m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i nho nh\u7887  \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean h\'e0nh lang \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7913  kia th\'e2n h\'ecnh kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9, \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i r\u7845 t l\u7899 n. V\u7915 a r\u7891 i trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn k\u297 , ch\u7881  l\u7901  m\u7901  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y tr\'ean g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \'f3 mang theo n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i cong l\'ean, con m\u7855 t l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tr\'f2ng tr\u7855 ng, b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng theo d\'f5i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u7899  t\u7899 i \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u7907 c linh \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i trong nh\'e0 t\u7855 m h\u7891 i c\u7845 p ba n\u259 m \u273 \'f3, c\u361 ng l\'e0 khu\'f4n m\u7863 t m\u7901  nh\u7841 t tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch m\'e0 \u273 \u7901  \u273 \u7851 n, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u432 \u7907 ng kh\u7855 c trong ch\'f9a, v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n to\'e9t mi\u7879 ng c\u432 \u7901 i, b\u7845 t k\u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n g\'f3c \u273 \u7897  n\'e0o, n\'f3 \u273 \u7873 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tim c\uc0\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c treo ng\u432 \u7907 c, h\'e9t l\u7899 n m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "Ai!" \u272 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c soi \u273 \'e8n v\u7873  ph\'eda \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7883  \'e1nh s\'e1ng chi\u7871 u \u273 \u7871 n, th\u7913  kia ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng c\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec c\u7911 a b\'e9 g\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e0m sao v\uc0\u7853 y?" T\u7915  l\u7847 u m\u7897 t truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng h\u7887 i c\u7911 a ch\u7911  tr\u7885 , ti\u7871 p theo l\'e0 thanh \'e2m k\u7869 o k\u7865 t k\u7869 o k\u7865 t l\'ean l\u7847 u, sau \u273 \'f3 "T\'e1ch" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, \u273 \'e8n h\'e0nh lang \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7853 t l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n th\u7845 y r\'f5 kia l\'e0 g\'ec. \u272 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t b\'e9 g\'e1i kho\u7843 ng b\u7843 y, t\'e1m tu\u7893 i, tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 eo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841  l\u7899 n m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng nh\u432  em b\'e9 trong tranh T\u7871 t. Kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng m\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t n\u7841  kia h\u432 \u7899 ng l\'ean tr\'ean, n\'e9t m\u7863 t t\u432 \u417 i c\u432 \u7901 i, l\'f4ng m\'e0y r\u7845 t m\u7843 nh, con m\u7855 t r\u7845 t l\u7899 n, nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 tr\'f2ng tr\u7855 ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 con ng\u432 \u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  k\'e9o b\'e9 g\'e1i v\'e0o l\'f2ng, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng m\u7855 ng: "O\'e1nh O\'e1nh, sao con kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  l\u7841 i ch\u7841 y l\'ean \u273 \'e2y? M\u7865  \u273 \'e2u r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 b\'e9 th\'e1o m\uc0\u7863 t n\u7841  xu\u7889 ng, chu m\'f4i v\u7899 i cha: "M\u7865  ng\u7911  r\u7891 i, con kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  l\u7841 i n\'f3i c\'f4 b\'e9 v\'e0i c\'e2u, l\u7845 y m\u7863 t n\u7841  l\u7841 i r\u7891 i xua c\'f4 b\'e9 \u273 i ng\u7911 , nh\'ecn con g\'e1i m\'ecnh xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t m\u7899 i quay qua Tr\'ec Di\'ean, x\u7845 u h\u7893  n\'f3i: "Th\u7853 t s\u7921  xin l\u7895 i, con g\'e1i t\'f4i r\u7845 t ngh\u7883 ch ng\u7907 m. B\u7903 i v\'ec v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\'e1ch n\'ean qu\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \u273 \'e8n, c\'f3 l\'e0m c\u7853 u s\u7907  kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3, kh\'f4ng vi\uc0\u7879 c g\'ec." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, nh\'ecn m\u7863 t n\u7841  trong tay \'f4ng ch\u7911 , "Kia l\'e0 g\'ec v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e0 *na di\uc0\u7879 n, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m *nh\u7843 y na s\u7869  d\'f9ng. Trong th\'f4n ch\'fang ta h\u7847 u nh\u432  m\u7895 i nh\'e0 \u273 \u7873 u c\u7845 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t con b\'e9 l\'e0m c\'e1ch n\'e0o m\'e0 l\u7845 y ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c." \'d4ng ch\u7911  gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'f3i, "Th\'f4n ch\'fang ta trong l\u7877  m\u7915 ng n\u259 m m\u7899 i s\u7869  nh\u7843 y na, l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i nghi l\u7877 ."\cb1 \

