\f1\i0  . Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u phong t\u7909 c v\'e0 h\'ecnh th\u7913 c s\'f9ng b\'e1i th\u7847 n linh n\'e0y ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n th\u7883 nh h\'e0nh \u7903  khu v\u7921 c s\'f4ng C\'e1m, th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R \u7903  ph\u432 \u417 ng b\u7855 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i c\'f3 nghi th\u7913 c t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 . C\u7853 u nh\u7899  t\u7899 i tin t\u7913 c s\u432  ph\u7909  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m n\'f3i cho b\u7885 n c\u7853 u, ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia l\'e0 t\u7915  ph\'eda nam d\u7901 i t\u7899 i nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c, nh\u432  th\u7871  chuy\u7879 n c\'e1c th\'f4n d\'e2n mang t\u7853 p t\u7909 c kia t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y v\u7853 y d\u7877  hi\u7875 u r\u7891 i. V\u7873  ph\u7847 n nguy\'ean nh\'e2n di d\'e2n th\'ec c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia \u273 a s\u7889  l\'e0 v\'ec thi\'ean tai nh\'e2n h\u7885 a, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  h\u7841 n h\'e1n l\u361  l\u7909 t ho\u7863 c chi\u7871 n lo\u7841 n; sau khi x\'e2y d\u7921 ng \u273 \u7845 t n\u432 \u7899 c th\'ec ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n do y\u7871 u t\u7889  ch\'ednh s\'e1ch. Song b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i t\'ecm hi\u7875 u th\'f4n d\'e2n v\'ec sao n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 d\u7901 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan g\'ec t\u7899 i tung t\'edch nh\'e0 Chu Huy v\'e0 hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  tr\u7885  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng l\u7841 i l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i, n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7891 i c\u7847 m m\u7863 t n\u7841  \u273 i kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7915 a v\'e0o ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh kh\'f3a c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7911  th\'ec ch\u7907 t nghe th\u7845 y ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a vang l\'ean ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a khe kh\u7869 . Ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a vang l\'ean ba l\u7847 n, th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a l\u7841 i g\'f5 ba c\'e1i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m kia nghe c\'f3 \uc0\u273 i\u7875 m k\u7923  qu\'e1i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ti\u7871 ng vang k\u7923  qu\'e1i m\'e0 l\'e0 v\u7883  tr\'ed ph\'e1t ra \'e2m thanh. Ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a s\u7869  g\'f5 \u7903  gi\u7919 a, \'e2m thanh ph\'e1t ra t\u7915  n\u417 i \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng l\u7847 n n\'e0y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng l\u7841 i ph\'e1t ra t\u7915  ph\u7847 n d\u432 \u7899 i c\u7917 a, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang n\u7857 m tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t g\'f5\'97\'97 n\u7857 m r\u7841 p tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, v\u7915 a nh\'ecn xuy\'ean qua khe c\u7917 a b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i nh\'f2m v\'e0o trong, v\u7915 a th\'f2 tay g\'f5.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean cau m\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  khi \u273 i v\'e0o th\'f4n n\'e0y, c\u7853 u lu\'f4n th\u7845 y c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u7893  qu\'e1i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i n\'ean l\u7901 i. Nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7895  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\u7847 m m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c ph\'f9 tr\u7915  t\'e0 trong tay, v\u7863 n m\u7903  kh\'f3a, k\'e9o c\u7917 a ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y m\uc0\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 \'e8n h\'e0nh lang s\'e1ng l\'ean, c\'f3 th\u7875  r\'f5 r\'e0ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i nho nh\u7887  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a, l\'e0 c\'f4 b\'e9 O\'e1nh O\'e1nh l\'fac n\'e3y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 b\'e9 d\'e1ng ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i th\u7845 p, tr\'e1ch kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u417 i g\'f5 c\u7917 a c\u361 ng l\'e0 b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong tay c\'f4 b\'e9 \'f4m hai con b\'fap b\'ea v\uc0\u7843 i, nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7903  c\u7917 a li\u7873 n ng\u7917 a \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, s\u7907  h\'e3i n\'f3i: "V\u7915 a r\u7891 i ch\'fa b\u7883  con d\u7885 a s\u7907  sao? V\u7853 y con \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i em trai em g\'e1i c\'f9ng ch\'fa \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?" C\'f4 b\'e9 n\'f3i xong gi\u417  hai con b\'fap b\'ea trong ng\u7921 c l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i b\'fap b\'ea c\'f3 k\'edch th\u432 \u7899 c gi\u7889 ng nhau, m\u7897 t trai m\u7897 t g\'e1i, c\u7905  b\u7857 ng c\'e1nh tay \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh, nh\'ecn qua d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m th\u7911  c\'f4ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng v\u7909 ng v\u7873 , gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  do tr\u7867  con t\u7921  m\'ecnh kh\'e2u v\'e1. N\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\'f4 b\'e9 n\'e0y t\u7921  m\'ecnh may th\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean \u7913 ng \u273 \u7889 i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o. C\u7853 u c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "C\u7843 m \u417 n con, ch\'fa kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i ch\'fa kh\'f4ng b\u7883  h\'f9 \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\u7915  ch\u7889 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, c\'f4 b\'e9 v\u7851 n gi\u417  hai con b\'fap b\'ea v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7917 a \u273 \'eam \u273 \'e3 khuya, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'e1c, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i nh\u7853 n l\u7845 y, d\u7863 n d\'f2 c\'f4 b\'e9 \u273 i ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 O\'e1nh O\'e1nh th\uc0\u7845 y c\u7853 u nh\u7853 n b\'fap b\'ea r\u7891 i li\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i vui v\u7867 , nh\u7843 y ch\'e2n s\'e1o \u273 i xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  h\u7859 n l\'e0 v\u7851 n \u273 ang tr\'f4ng coi \u7903  qu\u7847 y, th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  n\'e0y l\'e0m c\'e1ch n\'e0o m\'e0 qua m\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c cha ch\u7841 y l\'ean l\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f3a c\u7917 a, \u273 \u7863 t hai con b\'fap b\'ea l\'ean m\u7863 t b\'e0n tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng trong ph\'f2ng. D\'f9 sao ch\u7901  b\u7885 n h\u7885  tra\u777  ph\'f2ng xong, ch\u7911  tr\u7885  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  mang ch\'fang \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t l\'e0 do \u7843 o gi\'e1c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u hay ch\u7881  l\'e0 do c\u7853 u qu\'e1 l\u7841 nh, trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t khi nh\u7853 n hai con b\'fap b\'ea kia, c\u7853 u l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u7845 m \'e1p nh\u432  da ng\u432 \u7901 i. C\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'f3 tr\'f4i qua t\u7913 c th\'ec, c\u7853 u c\u7847 m tr\'ean tay, \u273 \u7863 t xu\u7889 ng b\'e0n, n\'f3 v\u7851 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 hai con b\'fap b\'ea v\u7843 i r\'e1ch n\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c may th\u7911  c\'f4ng s\u417  s\'e0i.\cb1 \
