\f9 \cf4 Ch\uc0\u432 \u417 ng 99: Mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \u7873 u d\u7853 y l\'fac b\u7843 y gi\u7901 . \u272 \u7875  ti\u7871 t ki\u7879 m th\u7901 i gian, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh chia th\'e0nh hai \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 i t\u7915  t\'e2y sang \u273 \'f4ng nghe ng\'f3ng tin t\u7913 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i t\u7915  \u273 \'f4ng sang t\'e2y \u273 i\u7873 u tra manh m\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua kh\'f4ng g\u7885 i v\u7873  nh\'e0, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n c\'f3 ph\u7847 n kh\'f4ng y\'ean t\'e2m \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, v\u7915 a \u273 i v\u7915 a \u273 \u7875  \'fd khung c\u7843 nh xung quanh, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i t\'ecm n\u417 i c\'f3 s\'f3ng t\u7889 t g\u7885 i v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i y\'ean t\u297 nh, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai \u273 i qua, c\'f2n c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u nh\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7887  ch\u7881  \u273 \u7911  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e1t \u273 \'e1 xanh, t\u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7855 ng m\'e1i xanh, phong c\'e1ch x\'e2y d\u7921 ng tuy kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t nh\u432 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  r\u7845 t c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\'f4n tr\u7845 n v\'f9ng C\'e1m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\u7843  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng c\u7845 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\'e0o t\'fai, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean ch\u7907 t th\u7845 y b\'ean ph\u7843 i con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 x\'e2y m\u7897 t ng\'f4i mi\u7871 u m\'e0u x\'e1m \u273 en c\u7921 c k\'ec trang nghi\'eam, ngay tr\'ean c\u7917 a ra v\'e0o kh\u7855 c ba ch\u7919 : "Mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na " .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i chi\u7871 c na di\u7879 n \u273 \'eam qua. Th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia c\'f3 truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng nh\u7843 y na, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  c\'f3 mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na. B\'ean ngo\'e0i mi\u7871 u, hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a g\u7895  r\u7845 t l\u7899 n m\'e0u \u273 en kh\'e9p h\u7901 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Mi\uc0\u7871 u th\u7847 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, ba m\u7863 t t\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u7917 a s\u7893 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 \'e1nh s\'e1ng xuy\'ean v\'e0o t\u7915  c\u7917 a t\'f2 v\'f2 n\'ean c\'f3 v\u7867  \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \'e2m u. Ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a mi\u7871 u th\u7901  m\u7897 t b\u7913 c t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n Na, kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ra l\'e0 l\'e0m b\u7857 ng v\u7853 t li\u7879 u g\'ec, b\'ean ngo\'e0i ph\u7911  m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o cho\'e0ng m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  l\'e0m b\u7857 ng g\u7845 m gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7891  h\'f3a trang, tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 eo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c na di\u7879 n m\'e0u v\'e0ng \u273 en, t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng to l\u7899 n s\u7915 ng s\u7919 ng nh\u432  t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7845 y trong ch\'f9a, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i th\u7845 p b\'e9 nh\u7887  ng\u432 \u7901 i, \'e1o cho\'e0ng m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  ph\u7889 i v\u7899 i na di\u7879 n m\'e0u \u273 en, c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 n v\'e0o, tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng th\u7847 n linh, gi\u7889 ng qu\u7927  d\u7919 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7853 t m\'ecnh, qua v\'e0i gi\'e2y m\u7899 i k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 \u7913 ng nguy\'ean t\u7841 i ch\u7895  v\'e1i t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901 . \'c1nh m\u7855 t c\u7853 u d\u7901 i l\'ean, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y ph\'eda tr\'ean t\u432 \u7907 ng treo m\u7897 t b\u7913 c m\'e0n m\'e0u xanh, tr\'ean \u273 \'f3 th\'eau b\u7889 n ch\u7919  l\u7899 n m\'e0u v\'e0ng " Th\'e1i T\u7917  Th\u7847 n Na " . L\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i nh\u7853 n ra, th\u7847 n Na n\'e0y h\'ecnh nh\u432  m\u7897 t \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7917 , t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7871  t\u7841 o theo v\'f3c d\'e1ng b\'e9 trai cho n\'ean tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn m\u7899 i th\u7845 p b\'e9 nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\'f9i l\u7841 i m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i nh\'ecn qua b\'ean tr\'e1i, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i l\u7841 i gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh. Ch\u7881  th\u7845 y m\u7845 y ch\u7909 c khu\'f4n m\u7863 t \u273 \u7873 u \u273 ang \u273 \u7891 ng lo\u7841 t h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng nh\u7871 ch l\'ean, m\u7863 t m\'e0y t\u432 \u417 i c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Nh\u7919 ng g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t kia m\u7863 t m\u361 i k\'edch c\u7905  kh\'e1c nhau, c\'f3 m\u7863 t th\u7847 n ho\u7863 c qu\u7927  m\'e0u xanh \u273 en \u273 \u7887 , c\u361 ng c\'f3 m\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i da tr\u7855 ng b\u7879 ch ho\u7863 c g\u7847 n gi\u7889 ng m\'e0u da ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\'f3 m\u7855 t c\'f3 con ng\u432 \u417 i, c\u361 ng c\'f3 m\u7855 t ch\u7881  c\'f3 tr\'f2ng tr\u7855 ng, n\u7871 u nh\'ecn k\u7929  c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n bi\u7875 u l\u7897  tr\'ean nh\u7919 ng g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t kia c\u361 ng c\'f3 kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t r\u7845 t nh\u7887 , nh\u432 ng t\u7845 t c\u7843  kh\'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\u7879  \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng cong l\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'eam qua Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  c\'f4 b\'e9 \u7903  nh\'e0 tr\u7885  d\u7885 a m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  nhanh ch\'f3ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 na di\u7879 n, c\u7843  m\u7863 t t\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u treo ch\'fang. Nh\u432 ng d\'f9 bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\u7863 t n\u7841 , \u7903  trong mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n \'e2m u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y nhi\u7873 u m\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u7853 u v\u7851 n s\u7903 n h\u7871 t gai \u7889 c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai tay m\'ecnh \u273 ang n\u7893 i da g\'e0 t\u7915 ng tr\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn qua t\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean ph\u7843 i, m\u7863 t t\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean \u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i tr\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, ch\u7881  d\'f9ng m\'e0n m\'e0u s\u7855 c r\u7921 c r\u7905  trang tr\'ed, nh\u7919 ng b\u7913 c m\'e0n \u273 \'f3 m\'e0u s\u7855 c \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t m\u7899 i, r\'f5 r\'e0ng m\u7899 i thay kh\'f4ng l\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m m\u7915 ng n\u259 m m\u7899 i s\u7869  nh\u7843 y na, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7893 i v\'e0o d\u7883 p \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\uc0\u7915 ng l\u7841 i l\'e2u th\'eam, v\'e1i t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n Na xong c\u361 ng v\'e1i hai b\'ean tr\'e1i ph\u7843 i r\u7891 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng quay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i ra, tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac b\u432 \u7899 c ra c\u7917 a mi\u7871 u l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nh\u432  c\'f3 gai \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o l\u432 ng, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  ph\'eda b\'ean ph\u7843 i sau l\u432 ng m\u7845 y ch\u7909 c \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7873 u \u273 ang nh\'ecn c\u7853 u ch\'f2ng ch\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ra kh\uc0\u7887 i mi\u7871 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng m\'e0 l\u7845 y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ra, \u273 \'fang l\'fac ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\u7841 ch t\'edn hi\u7879 u, trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u vui m\u7915 ng, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng g\u7885 i v\u7873  nh\'e0, l\'fac n\'e0y c\'f3 l\u7869  \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i t\u7853 p th\u7875  d\u7909 c bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng xong \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\'e3o nh\'e2n gia ch\uc0\u7853 m ch\u7841 p, chu\'f4ng \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i vang n\u259 m l\u7847 n m\u7899 i ti\u7871 p m\'e1y. Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7887 i ngo\u7841 i m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n c\'f3 \u7893 n kh\'f4ng, b\'e1o cho ngo\u7841 i m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  v\u7873  mu\u7897 n, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ch\u7901  c\u7853 u, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i c\u7913  ng\u7911  tr\u432 \u7899 c. C\u7853 u v\u7915 a n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai c\'e2u, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i l\u7841 i m\u7845 t s\'f3ng ng\u7855 t cu\u7897 c g\u7885 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  c\u7845 t di \u273 \u7897 ng, xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i sang ch\u7895  kh\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, ch\u7907 t th\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng g\u7847 n nh\u432  d\'e1n s\'e1t v\'e0o m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 m\uc0\u7897 t b\'e0 l\'e3o cao ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n ng\u7921 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean, t\'f3c mu\u7889 i ti\'eau, m\u7863 c m\u7897 t b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o g\u7845 m th\'eau hoa ki\u7875 u c\u361 , ch\u7889 ng m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c qu\u7843 i tr\u432 \u7907 ng m\'e0u \u273 en, \u273 ang ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u h\'edp m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i g\uc0\u7885 i l\'e0 *l\'e3o ng\'f4 l\'e3o d\u297  c\u7853 p nh\'e2n chi l\'e3o, b\u7903 i v\'ec \'f4ng b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean khi g\u7863 p nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0 kh\'e1c b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\u361 ng s\u7869  \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t quan t\'e2m h\u7885 , l\u7853 p t\u7913 c v\u7897 i khom l\u432 ng n\'f3i: "B\'e0, con kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7909 ng v\'e0o b\'e0 ch\u7913 ?" C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd chuy\u7879 n b\'e0 l\'e3o \u273 \u7913 ng ph\'eda sau thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a d\u7885 a c\u7853 u nh\u7843 y d\u7921 ng.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (*l\'e3o ng\'f4 l\'e3o d\uc0\u297  c\u7853 p nh\'e2n chi l\'e3o: T\'f4n k\'ednh ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0 c\u7911 a m\'ecnh cho \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'e0 c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o h\'edp m\uc0\u7855 t c\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "C\u7853 u v\u7915 a g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n v\u7873  nh\'e0 \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac b\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n mang theo kh\u7849 u \'e2m r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng c\u7911 a v\'f9ng C\'e1m Nam, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\u105 \u771  m\'f4\u803 t l\'e1t m\u7899 i hi\u7875 u b\'e0 l\'e3o h\u7887 i g\'ec, c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "V\'e2ng, con g\u7885 i cho \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u7903  nh\'e0, \'f4ng \u7903  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh con kh\'f4ng y\'ean t\'e2m l\u7855 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o nghe xong g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, v\u7851 y tay v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, \'fd b\u7843 o Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng k\u7873  s\'e1t v\'e0o b\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f3 hi\u7875 u nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n l\'e0m theo. Kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch r\u7845 t g\u7847 n, c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7917 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'e0 truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n m\'f9i m\u7909 c n\'e1t m\'e0 ch\u7881  n\u259 m th\'e1ng r\u7845 t d\'e0i tr\'f4i qua m\u7899 i c\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng b\'e0 l\'e3o nh\u7887  l\u7841 i r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u. R\u7845 t kh\u7869 , gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u th\'ec th\u7847 m n\'f3i: "Thi\u7871 u ni\'ean nghe l\u7901 i b\'e0 b\'e0 n\'f3i, th\u7915 a d\u7883 p c\'f2n s\u7899 m \u273 i nhanh \u273 i, \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7875  \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i ch\u7901 . B\'e0 b\'e0 l\'e0 ch\u7871 t gi\'e0, b\'e0 b\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a b\'e0 r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng, thanh \'e2m v\u7915 a nh\u7887  v\u7915 a kh\'f4ng r\'f5. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng nghe r\'f5 b\'e0 n\'f3i g\'ec, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c m\'ecnh c\'f3 nghe \u273 \'fang hay kh\'f4ng. C\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y sau l\u432 ng l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh, l\'fac ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean th\'ec b\'e0 l\'e3o \u273 \'e3 ch\u7889 ng qu\u7843 i tr\u432 \u7907 ng l\u7897 p c\u7897 p \u273 i xa, r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t \u7903  g\'f3c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, t\u7921  tr\u7845 n an n\'f3i nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 m\'ecnh nghe l\u7847 m r\u7891 i. C\'e1ch g\u7847 n v\u7853 y l\u7841 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n th\u7901 i gian l\'e2u nh\u432  th\u7871 , n\u7871 u b\'e0 l\'e3o kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh m\'ecnh s\u7869  nh\u7853 n ra. B\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i th\u7871  c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n khuy\'ean m\'ecnh n\'ean ch\u259 m s\'f3c \u7903  b\'ean ngo\u7841 i nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n, \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi kh\'f4ng c\'f2n r\u7891 i l\u7841 i h\u7889 i h\u7853 n, mu\u7889 n ph\u7909 ng d\u432 \u7905 ng m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 i d\u7841 o qua m\u7897 t v\'f2ng kh\'f4ng thu ho\u7841 ch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec, \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u, gi\u7901  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u v\'ec sao \'f4ng ch\u7911  tr\u7885  v\u7851 n c\'f2n ch\u417 i m\'e1y ch\u417 i game ki\u7875 u c\u361  kia. Kh\'f4ng li\'ean l\u7841 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, nh\'ecn th\u7901 i gian \u273 \'e3 m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901  g\u7847 n gi\u7919 a tr\u432 a, c\u7853 u quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh quay v\u7873  nh\'e0 tr\u7885  ch\u7901  h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\'fac tr\uc0\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 i ngang qua c\u7893 ng th\'f4n, c\u7853 u tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\'f9ng ch\u7911  ti\u7879 m t\u7841 p h\'f3a h\'f4m qua \u273 ang ng\u7891 i h\'fat thu\u7889 c n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n phi\u7871 m. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i qua, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\u7869  l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, \'fd n\'f3i kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng ti\u7871 p chuy\u7879 n v\'e0i c\'e2u, h\u7887 i: "\'d4ng ch\u7911 , t\'f4i th\u7845 y b\'ean kia c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\'e1i mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na, r\u7845 t th\'fa v\u7883 , \u7903  \u273 \'e2y m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7843 y na l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  ti\u7879 m m\u7903  c\u7917 a h\'e0ng bu\'f4n b\'e1n, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean r\u7845 t bi\u7871 t c\'e1ch n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, nghe v\u7853 y b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u thao thao b\u7845 t tuy\u7879 t: "Ta bi\u7871 t th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\u7853 p t\u7909 c n\'e0y, hai c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i th\'f4n ch\'fang ta \u273 \u7873 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7913 ng th\'fa v\u7899 i c\'e1i n\'e0y. Nh\u7843 y na ch\u7911  y\u7871 u l\'e0 \u273 \u7875  xua ma qu\u7927  tr\u7915  \'f4n d\u7883 ch, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  th\'e1ng gi\'eang m\u7895 i ng\'e0y nh\u7843 y t\u7915  s\'e1ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'eam, ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7843 y na \u273 eo na di\u7879 n t\u432 \u7907 ng tr\u432 ng cho qu\u7927  th\u7847 n, tr\u432 \u7899 c v\'e0 sau khi th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n nghi l\u7877  \u273 \u7873 u ph\u7843 i v\'e0o trong mi\u7871 u b\'e1i Th\'e1i T\u7917  th\u7847 n Na. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\'f2n c\'f3 nghi th\u7913 c so\'e1t na, ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7843 y na c\u7847 m \u273 \'e8n d\u7847 u \u273 i t\u7915 ng nh\'e0 "so\'e1t na", tr\u7909 c xu\u7845 t ma t\'e0 v\'e0 b\u7879 nh d\u7883 ch."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ngh\u297  t\u7899 i m\'ecnh v\'e0 \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p ma, nghe v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i hi\u7871 u k\u7923  n\'f3i: "C\'e1i n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7875  di\u7879 t tr\u7915  ma qu\u7927  sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  ti\u7879 m nghe v\u7853 y l\u7841 i tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c, h\'fat m\u7897 t h\u417 i thu\u7889 c th\u7853 t d\'e0i, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i nh\u7843  kh\'f3i, v\u7913 t \u273 \u7847 u thu\u7889 c l\'e1 xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t di d\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n r\u7891 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn m\u7897 t v\'f2ng xung quanh, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng nh\'ecn T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, h\u7841  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \u7845 y. Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m m\u7915 ng n\u259 m m\u7899 i n\u259 m nay \u273 \'e3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\u7909 c so\'e1t ra \'e1c qu\u7927 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nghe v\u7853 y c\u7843  kinh, th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\'e1ng c\u7911 a \'f4ng ch\u7911  ti\u7879 m c\u361 ng h\u417 i khi\u7871 p s\u7907 , ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y s\u7889 ng l\u432 ng n\u7893 i l\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o. H\u7855 n c\u361 ng c\u7849 n th\u7853 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i: "N\u7871 u t\'ecm ra th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o? C\'f3 \u273 u\u7893 i \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? \u272 u\u7893 i \u273 i \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3 na di\uc0\u7879 n. Thu ph\u7909 c \'e1c qu\u7927  v\'e0o trong na di\u7879 n, \'e1c qu\u7927  b\u7883  phong \u7845 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m m\u7903  to hai m\u7855 t, kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "C\'f3 c\u7843  c\'e1ch n\'e0y sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, \'fd b\u7843 o m\'ecnh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  ti\u7879 m c\'f2n t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 ang h\u7887 i m\'ecnh, th\u7853 t th\'e0 c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "L\u7841 i n\'f3i ti\u7871 p, th\u7853 t ra t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\'f4i \u7903  th\'f4n Th\u7841 ch Ph\u432 \u417 ng, sau khi l\u7845 y v\u7907  t\'f4i m\u7899 i \u273 i theo v\u7907  \u273 \u7883 nh c\u432  \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i t\u7915  t\u7915  hi\u7875 u r\'f5. M\u7899 i \u273 i xem nghi l\u7877  m\u7845 y l\u7847 n, nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7859 n l\'e0 hi\u7875 u l\u7855 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i th\'eam \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec n\u7919 a, mua th\'eam m\u7897 t bao thu\u7889 c r\u7891 i c\'e1o t\u7915  ch\u7911  ti\u7879 m, c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i b\u7897  v\u7873  nh\'e0 tr\u7885  \u259 n c\u417 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i trong th\'f4n kh\'f4ng g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng ch\'fa \'fd, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u259 n m\u7897 t b\'e0n, gia \u273 \'ecnh \'f4ng ch\u7911  tr\u7885  \u259 n \u7903  m\u7897 t b\'e0n kh\'e1c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y v\u7907  \'f4ng ch\u7911 , l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  g\u7847 y y\u7871 u nh\'ecn h\u417 i t\'e1i nh\u7907 t, l\'f4ng m\'e0y lu\'f4n nh\'edu l\u7841 i nh\u432  c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n lo s\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 b\'e9 O\'e1nh O\'e1nh \uc0\u259 n qua qu\'fdt xong ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ch\u417 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7907  \u259 n xong li\u7873 n k\'e9o con g\'e1i kh\'f4ng kh\'f4ng t\'ecnh nguy\u7879 n \u273 i, c\'f4 b\'e9 tr\u7873  m\'f4i, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i \u273 i theo m\u7865 , tr\u432 \u7899 c khi \u273 i c\'f2n quay \u273 \u7847 u, c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7851 y tay v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  tr\u7885  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh thu d\u7885 n b\'e0n \u259 n, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nh\'e2n c\u417  h\u7897 i h\u7887 i h\u7855 n: "M\u7865  \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  nh\'ecn c\'f3 v\u7867  tinh th\u7847 n kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t l\u7855 m?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 ." \'d4ng ch\u7911  tr\u7885  ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda b\u7885 n h\u7885 , c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  n\'f3i, "\u272 \'e3 t\'ecm th\u7847 y thu\u7889 c V\u432 \u417 ng trong th\'f4n xem b\u7879 nh r\u7891 i, n\'f3i l\'e0 c\u417  th\u7875  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec, ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\'e2m b\u7879 nh."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n v\u7915 a lau b\'e0n v\u7915 a n\'f3i: "T\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n g\'ec x\u7843 y ra, t\u7915  khi \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m m\u7899 i v\u7907  t\'f4i b\u7855 t h\u7889 t ho\u7843 ng, n\'f3i l\'e0 b\'e0 \u7845 y c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ngo\'e0i O\'e1nh O\'e1nh h\'ecnh nh\u432  ch\'fang t\'f4i c\'f2n m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a con trai m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a con g\'e1i n\u7919 a. C\'f3 ai l\'e0m m\u7865  m\'e0 kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c con m\'ecnh ch\u7913 , t\'f4i \u273 ang \u273 \u7883 nh m\u7845 y ng\'e0y n\'e0y kh\'f4ng b\u7853 n r\u7897 n th\'ec nh\u7901  h\'e0ng x\'f3m gi\'fap tr\'f4ng O\'e1nh O\'e1nh v\'e0 nh\'e0 tr\u7885 , t\'f4i \u273 \u432 a v\u7907  l\'ean b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n tr\'ean th\u7883  tr\u7845 n kh\'e1m xem sao."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Hay l\'e0 l\'ean th\uc0\u7859 ng th\'e0nh ph\u7889  kh\'e1m \u273 i, b\u7879 nh v\u7873  tinh th\u7847 n kh\'f4ng d\u7877  kh\'e1m \u273 \'e2u." T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m n\'f3i ti\u7871 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i c\uc0\u361 ng mu\u7889 n nh\u432 ng m\'e0 qu\'e1 xa, \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\u7877  \u273 i. \u272 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 bao nhi\'eau n\u259 m r\u7891 i m\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ra v\'e0o th\'f4n v\u7851 n ch\u432 a tu s\u7917 a t\u7889 t." \'d4ng ch\u7911  tr\u7885  nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng o\'e1n tr\'e1ch, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ti\u7871 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i th\uc0\u7845 y m\u7845 y ng\'e0y nay kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7845 y ai \u273 \u7871 n ngh\u7881  ch\'e2n, bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u ch\'fang t\'f4i c\u361 ng s\u7869  \u273 i." T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m th\u7915 a c\u417  h\u7887 i, "L\'e3o b\u7843 n, m\u7845 y ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c th\'ec sao? Ngo\'e0i ch\'fang t\'f4i ra c\'f2n c\'f3 ai kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong th\'f4n ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'e0 tr\u7885 , n\u7871 u nh\'e0 Chu Huy ho\u7863 c hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia, v\u7853 y ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  tr\u7885  tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c m\u7897 t l\'e1t, b\'ecnh t\u297 nh nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 ang ngh\u297  g\'ec hay ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u273 ang nh\u7899  l\u7841 i nh\u7919 ng kh\'e1ch \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n m\u7845 y ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c. Sau m\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u h\u7855 n thu d\u7885 n m\'e2m tr\'ean b\'e0n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai \u273 \u7871 n. T\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  ch\u432 a c\'f3 ai t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'f4ng tin n\'e0y v\uc0\u7899 i th\'f4ng tin bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m th\u259 m d\'f2 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903  n\u417 i kh\'e1c gi\u7889 ng nhau, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng, g\u7885 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean hai ti\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n \u273 ang th\u7845 t th\u7847 n, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7895  vai c\u7853 u m\u7899 i ho\'e0n h\u7891 n, quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  h\u7855 n, ng\u432 ng tr\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng, ch\'fang ta ph\u7843 i ch\u7841 y kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y ngay, th\'f4n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u7903  l\u7841 i th\'eam \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, nghi ho\u7863 c n\'f3i: "L\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? C\u7853 u ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \'e0, hay v\u7915 a ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1i g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\'ecnh t\uc0\u297 nh nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, y\u7871 t h\u7847 u gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng xu\u7889 ng g\u7857 n t\u7915 ng ch\u7919 : "Trong th\'f4n c\'f3 qu\u7927 , m\u7845 u ch\u7889 t l\'e0, \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y t\'f4i ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ai l\'e0 qu\u7927 ."\cb1 \
