\f1\b0 \cf2 V\uc0\u7915 a r\u7891 i l\'fac \u259 n c\u417 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7899  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n ph\'e1t sinh bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng, h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u7915 ng chi ti\u7871 t, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7893  qu\'e1i \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  m\'ecnh xem nh\u7865 . Ngay sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c \'97\'97 b\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u kia, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i r\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 m\u7863 c m\u7897 t th\'e2n \'e1o li\u7879 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\u7915 ng theo \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\'e0 m\u7865  lo tang s\u7921  cho b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'f9ng \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i lo tang s\u7921  cho m\u7865 , \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng lo\u7841 i qu\u7847 n \'e1o kia nh\u7899  r\u7845 t r\'f5 ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m g\u7863 p l\'e3o b\'e0 c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i m\u7899 i gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh nh\u7853 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean nh\uc0\u7919 ng l\u7901 i b\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  nghe l\u7847 m, b\'e0 n\'f3i th\u7853 t cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, c\u361 ng c\u7843 nh b\'e1o c\u7853 u, b\u7843 o c\u7853 u nhanh ch\'f3ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i trong th\'f4n ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?" T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u259 ng th\u7859 ng, nh\'ecn v\'f4 c\'f9ng lo l\u7855 ng, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ho\'e0i nghi l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i: "C\uc0\u7853 u l\'ean ph\'f2ng l\u7845 y \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c \u273 i, t\'f4i n\'f3i v\u7899 i \'f4ng ch\u7911  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i ch\'fang ta s\u7869  \u273 i ngay. Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c trong th\'f4n hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i v\u7853 y, ch\u7881  d\u7921 a v\'e0o hai ch\'fang ta c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch g\'ec, \u273 \u7907 i sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  m\u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c cao nh\'e2n r\u7891 i t\'ednh ti\u7871 p."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921 , g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7853 u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y ch\u7901  t\'f4i, hai ph\'fat sau t\'f4i xu\u7889 ng ngay."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  tr\u7885  v\u7915 a r\u7891 i thu d\u7885 n b\'e0n \u259 n ra sau b\u7871 p, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  nh\'e0 \u259 n g\u7885 i hai ti\u7871 ng, \'f4ng ch\u7911  hai tay \u432 \u7899 t n\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915  sau b\u7871 p \u273 i ra, r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 ang r\u7917 a ch\'e9n \u273 \u361 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean thanh to\'e1n ti\uc0\u7873 n \u259 n cho h\u7855 n, tr\u7843  ph\'f2ng, \u273 \u7907 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m xu\u7889 ng giao ch\'eca kh\'f3a. K\u7871 t qu\u7843  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7907 i m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat v\u7851 n ch\u432 a th\u7845 y h\u7855 n xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u, mang xu\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, d\'f9 c\'f3 \u273 i v\u7879  sinh th\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ph\u7843 i quay l\u7841 i r\u7891 i. C\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng ng\u7891 i kh\'f4ng y\'ean, c\u7847 m kh\'f3a d\u7921  ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a \'f4ng ch\u7911  \u273 i l\'ean l\u7847 u t\'ecm T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7917 a ph\'f2ng \u273 ang kh\'e9p, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i v\'e0o li\u7873 n th\u7845 y t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 thu d\u7885 n xong \u273 \u7875  \u7903  trong t\'fai, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7841 i \u273 ang n\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 ng\u7845 t \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i nhanh t\u7899 i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7855 c l\u7855 c h\u7855 n, g\u7885 i t\'ean: "T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, c\u7853 u l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y? Mau t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i!"\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7907 t l\u7841 nh, nh\'ecn \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901  tr\u432 a, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed th\u7883 nh nh\u7845 t trong ng\'e0y. M\'e0 qua m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901 , d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed s\u7869  c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng y\u7871 u, \'e2m kh\'ed s\u7869  c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng m\u7841 nh, kh\'f4ng nh\'e2n l\'fac n\'e0y r\u7901 i \u273 i ch\u7881  s\u7907  s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a. T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 ang y\'ean l\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean h\'f4n m\'ea, c\'e0ng ch\u7913 ng t\u7887  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 mu\u7889 n b\u7855 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u7903  l\u7841 i ch\u7895  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y h\u7841  quy\u7871 t t\'e2m, tay tr\'e1i c\u7847 m \u273 \u7891 , tay ph\u7843 i d\'ecu T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \u7905  h\u7855 n ra c\u7917 a. T\u7845 t c\u7843  l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i hai con b\'fap b\'ea v\u7843 i tr\'ean b\'e0n h\'f4m nay \u273 \'e3 thi\u7871 u \u273 i m\u7897 t con.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean mang theo T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m xu\u7889 ng l\u7847 u, \'f4ng ch\u7911  tr\u7885  th\u7845 y T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m h\'f4n m\'ea b\u7845 t t\u7881 nh c\u361 ng l\u7855 p b\u7855 p kinh h\'e3i, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n gi\'fap n\'e2ng h\u7855 n h\u7887 i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh, c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7907 i th\'eam ch\u7889 c l\'e1t, h\u7855 n \u273 i m\u7901 i th\u7847 y thu\u7889 c V\u432 \u417 ng t\u7899 i xem.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u7903  l\u7841 i th\'eam n\u7919 a. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m th\'e0nh ra th\u7871  n\'e0y, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i do b\u7879 nh m\'e0 do ma qu\u7927  qu\u7845 y ph\'e1, nhanh ch\'f3ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i th\'f4n n\'e0y l\'e0 l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u t\u7915  ch\u7889 i kh\'e9o \'fd t\u7889 t c\u7911 a \'f4ng ch\u7911 , ch\u7881  nh\u7901  h\u7855 n t\'ecm gi\'fap m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c d\'e2y th\u7915 ng d\'e0i ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n, sau \u273 \'f3 d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  tr\u7907  gi\'fap c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7905  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\'ean ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i ph\'eda sau xe m\'e1y, d\'f9ng d\'e2y th\u7915 ng bu\u7897 c hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i. \u272 \u7847 u T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m g\u7889 i l\'ean vai Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u432  v\u7853 y nh\u7901  d\'e2y th\u7915 ng bu\u7897 c l\u7841 i h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7883  ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7843 i qua m\u7897 t h\u7891 i n\'e0y, di \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 n th\u7883  m\u7897 t gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u. \u272 \u432 \u7901 ng ra v\'e0o th\'f4n ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t. Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u c\'e1o bi\u7879 t \'f4ng ch\u7911 , \u273 i xe d\u7885 c tr\u7903  l\u7841 i con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'fac \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m nay tr\uc0\u7901 i \u273 \u7847 y m\'e2y, t\u7915  s\'e1ng s\u7899 m \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  ch\u432 a th\u7845 y m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i, trong n\'fai l\u7841 i n\u7893 i s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9, c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng d\'e0y, c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng l\u7841 nh, m\u7883 t m\u7901  gi\u259 ng k\'edn con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\uc0\u7871 t kh\'ed tr\u7901 i c\'f9ng s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 n\'e0y kh\'f4ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, ch\u7881  e kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p. Nh\u432 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7889 t m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9 d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u7903  ng\'e3 ba kia, l\'fac n\'e0y trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u nh\u432  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7881  d\u7851 n, n\u7855 m r\'f5 h\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7883  c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t l\'e0m cho m\'ea mu\u7897 i l\u7841 c l\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i ch\u7915 ng m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat, m\u7855 t th\u7845 y chi\u7871 c xe ba b\'e1nh g\u7863 p l\'fac \u273 i \u273 \'e3 c\'e1ch b\u7885 n h\u7885  ng\'e0y c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7907 t c\u7843 m th\u7845 y sau g\'e1y l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7841 nh ng\u7855 t c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901  d\'e1n sau l\u432 ng m\'ecnh, s\u7913 c n\u7863 ng \u273 \'e8 tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng l\u7899 n. B\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7901 i ti\u7871 t r\u7845 t l\u7841 nh, to\'e0n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p l\u7841 nh c\'f3ng, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean kh\'f4ng nh\u7841 y, nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t gi\'e1c ra c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u h\'f4 l\'ean "T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m?", \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i gi\u7919  ch\u7855 c tay l\'e1i nhanh ch\'f3ng quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3 thi\u7871 u ch\'fat n\u7919 a ng\'e3 ra kh\u7887 i xe \'97\'97 \u273 \'e2u c\'f2n T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, n\u7857 m sau l\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\'e0 m\u7897 t con ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  hai m\u7855 t l\'f2i ra, l\u432 \u7905 i k\'e9o d\'e0i. Hai tay ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  kia b\'e1m l\u7845 y c\u7893  c\u7853 u, c\u432 \u7901 i qu\'e1i \u273 \u7843 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac gi\uc0\u7919 a tr\u432 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\'f4n kia b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng li\u7873 n chu\u7849 n b\u7883  r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ph\'f9 tr\u7915  t\'e0 c\u7845 t trong t\'fai. L\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u v\u7897 i v\'e0ng d\u7915 ng xe, hai tay tr\'e1i ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7873 u c\u7847 m m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9, m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ch\u7881  l\'ean tr\u7901 i, m\u7897 t t\u7845 m d\'e1n v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c ti\u7875 u qu\u7927 . Ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m g\'ec, b\u7883  c\u7853 u d\'e1n tr\'fang, nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i v\u7853 y l\u7841 i tr\u7903  n\'ean hung \'e1c, hai b\'e0n tay nh\u7887  nh\u432  \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9 b\'f3p ch\u7863 t c\u7893  Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i h\'e1 m\u7891 m c\u7855 n v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Mi\uc0\u7879 ng n\'f3 trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t tr\u7903  n\'ean c\u7921 c l\u7899 n, to\'e9t \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n mang tai, trong mi\u7879 ng m\u7885 c chi ch\'edt r\u259 ng nh\u7885 n h\'ecnh tam gi\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7845 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng, d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh th\u7871  c\u7845 p b\'e1ch li\u7873 n c\u7855 n l\'ean ng\'f3n tr\u7887  tay tr\'e1i\'97\'97 m\'e1u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u l\'e0 t\'e0 kh\'ed m\u7841 nh nh\u7845 t trong c\u417  th\u7875 , r\u7845 t thu\u7847 n t\'fay. T\'e0 kh\'ed \u7903  nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i kh\'e1c trong c\u417  th\u7875  ch\u7881  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7893  v\'e0o, ch\u7881  tr\'f4i \u7903  b\u7873  ngo\'e0i, kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  b\u7903 i c\u7853 u; nh\u432 ng t\'e0 kh\'ed trong m\'e1u l\u7841 i nh\u7853 p th\u7859 ng v\'e0o trong huy\u7871 t m\u7841 ch, v\'f4 c\'f9ng thu\u7847 n t\'fay ngang ng\u432 \u7907 c, ma qu\u7927  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngay th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u s\u7855 p c\u7855 n l\'ean ng\'f3n tay, m\u7897 t d\'f2ng kh\'ed \u273 en \u273 \u7863 c \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tu\'f4n ra t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c c\u7853 u, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c h\u7845 t ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  kia xu\u7889 ng. \u272 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i m\u7897 t ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a m\'e0u \u273 en b\'f9ng ch\'e1y tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3, ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  kia ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, \u7903  trong ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n k\'eau g\'e0o, v\'f4 c\'f9ng th\'ea l\u432 \u417 ng, ch\u7881  ch\u7889 c l\'e1t \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7885 n l\u7917 a \u273 en v\u7851 n ch\u432 a d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i m\'e0 ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ch\'e1y. Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7845 y v\'f4 c\'f9ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng, th\u7913  \u273 ang b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 t trong l\u7917 a nh\'ecn c\u7921 c k\'ec quen m\u7855 t, ch\'ednh l\'e0 con b\'fap b\'ea v\u7843 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'e2u v\'e1 s\u417  s\'e0i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c. Ch\u7881  trong ph\'fat ch\u7889 c con b\'fap b\'ea \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 t th\'e0nh tro b\u7909 i, b\u7883  gi\'f3 th\u7893 i tan \u273 i, ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a theo \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng l\u7909 i t\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 a tay s\u7901  b\'ecnh s\u7913 , gi\u417  l\'ean b\'ean m\'f4i kh\u7869  h\'f4n. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5, l\u7841 i l\'e0 b\'ecnh s\u7913  n\'e0y, l\u7841 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i kia c\u7913 u m\'ecnh m\u7897 t m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a t\u7855 t, n\'e9t m\u7863 t ch\u7907 t bi\u7871 n, l\'ean xe, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\u7915 a t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng s\u7889 ng ch\u7841 y ra t\u7915  n\u417 i nguy hi\u7875 m, l\u7841 i quay \u273 \u7847 u l\'e1i xe ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u c\u7853 u ngh\u297  kh\'f4ng sai, nh\'e0 Chu Huy v\u7899 i hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia s\u7907  l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  c\u7913 u v\u7873  n\u7919 a, m\'e0 hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i n\u7871 u c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mau tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng qua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'eam nay, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u361 ng s\u7869  m\u7845 t m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e1i xe tr\uc0\u7903  l\u7841 i nh\'e0 tr\u7885 , \'f4ng ch\u7911  th\u7845 y c\u7853 u m\u7897 t m\'ecnh v\'f2ng v\u7873  r\u7845 t kinh ng\u7841 c: "Sao l\u7841 i tr\u7903  l\u7841 i r\u7891 i? Qu\'ean \u273 \u7891  \'e0? Anh b\u7841 n kia c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn \'f4ng ch\uc0\u7911  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng xe m\'e1y ch\u7841 y ra \u273 \'f3n, \'e1nh m\u7855 t t\u7889 i s\u7847 m l\u7841 i, tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c ph\'fat ch\u7889 c, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, \u273 \'e1p thu\u7853 n theo l\u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng: "V\'e2ng, t\'f4i \u273 \u7875  qu\'ean m\u7845 t c\u7909 c s\u7841 c, b\u7841 n t\'f4i \u273 ang kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 e n\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 i c\'f9ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  tr\u7885  nghe v\u7853 y li\u7873 n \u273 \u432 a ch\'eca kh\'f3a cho c\u7853 u: "V\u7853 y c\u7853 u ch\u7841 y l\'ean t\'ecm th\u7917  xem, t\'f4i c\u361 ng ch\u432 a k\u7883 p d\u7885 n ph\'f2ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, c\u7847 m ch\'eca kh\'f3a \u273 i l\'ean l\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng tr\uc0\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 b\'f3ng d\'e1ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 a m\u7855 t nh\'ecn chi\u7871 c b\'e0n duy nh\u7845 t trong ph\'f2ng, ph\'eda tr\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t con b\'fap b\'ea v\u7843 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\uc0\u7921  \u273 i t\u7899 i, c\u7855 n ng\'f3n tr\u7887  tay tr\'e1i, d\'f9ng m\'e1u m\'ecnh v\u7869  m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9 v\'e3ng sinh l\'ean con b\'fap b\'ea, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7845 y b\u7853 t l\u7917 a \u273 \u7889 t t\u7915  d\u432 \u7899 i l\'ean..\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7917 a n\'e0y d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 l\u7917 a ph\'e0m, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 uy l\u7921 c nh\u432  ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a \u273 en ban n\'e3y, trong ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a m\'e0u cam lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng la kh\'f3c \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n c\u7911 a b\'e9 g\'e1i, ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 b\'fap b\'ea v\u7843 i trong l\u7917 a bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh b\u7897  d\u7841 ng m\u7897 t n\u7919  \u273 \u7891 ng, c\u7921 c k\u7923  gi\u7889 ng ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f5ng tr\'ean vai l\'fac n\'e3y, hai m\u7855 t l\u7891 i l\'ean, h\'ecnh d\u7841 ng \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 . N\'f3 gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a mu\u7889 n \u273 \'e1nh v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i b\u7883  huy\u7871 t ph\'f9 v\u7869  tr\'ean c\u417  th\u7875  \u273 \u7883 nh th\'e2n t\u7841 i ch\u7895 , kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7853 y, \'e1nh m\u7855 t nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng th\'eam o\'e1n \u273 \u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean lui l\uc0\u7841 i m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, \'e1nh m\u7855 t qu\'e9t v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng, ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\'e2n \u7843 nh nho nh\u7887  \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 O\'e1nh O\'e1nh con g\'e1i ch\uc0\u7911  tr\u7885 , c\'f4 b\'e9 nh\'ecn \'e1nh l\u7917 a m\'e0u cam \u273 ang d\u7847 n t\u7855 t, c\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec, nh\u432 ng l\u7901 i n\'f3i ra l\u7841 i l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta s\u7903 n gai \u7889 c: "Ch\'fa, con \u273 em em trai em g\'e1i c\u7911 a con cho ch\'fa, v\'ec sao ch\'fa l\u7841 i gi\u7871 t ch\'fang?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'f5i theo n\'f3, tay s\uc0\u7901  l\'ean ph\'f9 tr\u7915  t\'e0 trong t\'fai \'e1o: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ch\'fa gi\u7871 t, l\'e0 con gi\u7871 t. T\u7841 i sao con l\u7841 i h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t em m\'ecnh, bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  b\u7883  con s\u7917  d\u7909 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean m\uc0\u7863 t c\u7911 a c\'f4 b\'e9 hi\u7879 n ra v\'e0i ph\u7847 n \u7845 m \u7913 c: "Cha m\u7865  \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i s\u7869  \u273 \u432 a con \u273 i ch\u417 i, mua b\'fap b\'ea cho con, nh\u432 ng sau khi c\'f3 em r\u7891 i h\u7885  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd con n\u7919 a. C\'f3 m\u7897 t h\'f4m con ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n d\'f9 con c\'f3 kh\'f3c th\u7871  n\'e0o h\u7885  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m, nh\u432 ng em v\u7915 a kh\'f3c cha m\u7865  \u273 \'e3 v\u7897 i \u273 \u7871 n. N\'ean con \u273 em em l\'e0m th\'e0nh b\'fap b\'ea c\u7911 a con, sau \u273 \'f3 khi\u7871 n ch\'fang c\u361 ng bi\u7871 n cha m\u7865  th\'e0nh nh\u432  con. Ch\'fang r\u7845 t nghe l\u7901 i m\'e0 \u273 i l\'e0m ngay."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong c\'e2u cu\uc0\u7889 i "C\'f4 b\'e9" ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u c\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o: "Nh\u432  v\u7853 y con s\u7869  c\'f3 b\'fap b\'ea, m\'e0 cha m\u7865  c\u361 ng s\u7869  \u273 \u7873 u quan t\'e2m con."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean, sau khi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n hai con b\'fap b\'ea v\u7843 i kia c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  b\u7883  \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9 cho c\u7853 u b\'fap b\'ea kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432  v\u7853 y hai v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng ch\u7911  tr\u7885  t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  s\u7889 ng c\'f9ng c\'f4 b\'e9 r\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\'e0 nh\u7919 ng th\'f4n d\'e2n kh\'e1c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n nh\'e0 tr\u7885  duy nh\u7845 t trong th\'f4n c\'f3 c\u7893  qu\'e1i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  bi\u7871 t c\u7843  nh\'e0 n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t... Trong th\'f4n n\'e0y, li\u7879 u c\'f3 c\'f2n ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f4 b\'e9 ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u "Em trai em g\'e1i \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n, v\u7853 y ch\'fa \u7903  l\u7841 i v\u7899 i O\'e1nh O\'e1nh \u273 i, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Ng\'f3n tr\uc0\u7887  tay tr\'e1i Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n \u273 ang ch\u7843 y m\'e1u, c\u7853 u b\'f4i t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\'e1u l\'ean hai t\u7845 m ph\'f9 trong t\'fai, t\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t \u273 i t\u7899 i c\u7917 a: "N\'f3i cho ch\'fa bi\u7871 t, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 ang \u7903  \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 O\'e1nh O\'e1nh l\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, ch\u7881  v\u7851 n c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "Ch\'fa \u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y \u273 i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng b\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\u7855 t \u273 i s\u7869  b\u7883  l\'e0m th\'e0nh na di\u7879 n \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7853 p m\u7841 nh m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0m th\'e0nh na di\uc0\u7879 n...\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, \u273 i t\u7899 i c\u7917 a b\'ean c\u7841 nh \'e1c qu\u7927 . Sau \u273 \'f3 d\'f9ng t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  nhanh nh\u7845 t c\u7847 m m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9 tr\u7915  t\'e0 d\'e1n l\'ean O\'e1nh O\'e1nh, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i quay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, \u273 \'f3ng c\'e1nh c\u7917 a n\u7863 ng n\u7873  sau l\u432 ng l\u7841 i, d\'e1n m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9 kh\'e1c l\'ean c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng nguy\u7873 n r\u7911 a c\'f9ng ti\u7871 ng g\'e0o th\'e9t th\'ea l\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a n\'f3 b\'ean trong c\'e1nh c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7855 c hai t\u7845 m ph\'f9 c\'f3 th\u7875  v\'e2y gi\u7919  con qu\u7927  kia bao l\'e2u, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 nh\'e0 c\u7911 a n\'f3, \u7893  c\u7911 a n\'f3, m\'e0 n\'f3 \u273 \'e3 l\u7845 y \'edt nh\u7845 t b\u7889 n m\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\'e1u d\'ednh tr\'ean tay \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n ru\u7897 t th\u7883 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  tr\u7885  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng li\u7873 n t\u7899 i h\u7887 i: "Sao th\u7871 ? T\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, \u7903  trong th\'f4n n\'e0y, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean m\u7845 t chuy\u7879 n hai \u273 \u7913 a con c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927 , v\u7851 n \u273 ang "s\u7889 ng" nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u432 a n\'f3i cho h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n th\u7915 a d\u7883 p tr\u432 \u7899 c khi con qu\u7927  tr\'ean l\u7847 u hai tho\'e1t ra ph\u7843 i mau ch\'f3ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m b\u7883  n\'f3 gi\u7845 u \u273 i, sau \u273 \'f3 d\'f9ng t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  nhanh nh\u7845 t mang b\u7841 n m\'ecnh r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y. Qu\u7927  c\u361 ng c\'f3 qu\'e1n t\'ednh khi c\'f2n s\u7889 ng, t\'e1m ch\'edn ph\u7847 n l\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7851 n \u273 ang b\u7883  gi\u7845 u trong nh\'e0 tr\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7907 t nh\'ecn th\u7845 y con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\u7901  b\u7909 i ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a nh\'e0 tr\u7885  c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i quen m\u7855 t \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng. D\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u417 i c\'f2ng, t\'f3c mu\u7889 i ti\'eau, m\u7897 t th\'e2n \'e1o li\u7879 m g\u7885 n g\'e0ng, ch\u7889 ng m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c qu\u7843 i tr\u432 \u7907 ng m\'e0u \u273 en \'97\'97 l\'e0 b\'e0 l\'e3o g\u7863 p ngo\'e0i mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o tr\'f4ng th\uc0\u7845 y c\u7853 u, v\u7851 y v\u7851 y tay v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, \'fd b\u7843 o c\u7853 u \u273 i ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  tr\u7885  \u273 ang quay l\u432 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7917 a, kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh b\'ean ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng do d\uc0\u7921 , cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n t\'ecm c\u7899  \u273 i ra kh\u7887 i nh\'e0 tr\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng t\u7841 i ch\u7895 , \u273 i r\u7845 t nhanh t\u7899 i g\'f3c r\u7869  \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  n\u417 i \u273 \'f3, v\u7851 n v\u7851 y tay v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ra hi\u7879 u c\u7853 u \u273 i t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
