\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\uc0\u297  ngh\u297 , nghi\u7871 n r\u259 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i \u273 i theo.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o nh\'ecn \uc0\u273 i kh\'f4ng v\u7919 ng, th\u7921 c t\u7871  l\u7841 i \u273 i r\u7845 t nhanh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\u7843 i ch\u7841 y b\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7887  m\u7899 i \u273 u\u7893 i k\u7883 p \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\'e0 l\'e3o \u273 i v\'e0o m\u7897 t c\u259 n nh\'e0 tr\u7879 t nh\u7887  \'e2m u \u273 \u417 n s\u417 , \u273 \u7913 ng trong ph\'f2ng v\u7851 y tay v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  v\u7851 y tay m\u7901 i v\'e0o nh\'e0, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean si\uc0\u7871 t ch\u7863 t chi\u7871 c ph\'f9 tr\u7915  t\'e0 c\'f2n l\u7841 i trong \'e1o, suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n b\u7845 t ch\u7845 p \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o v\uc0\u7851 n v\u7915 a l\u7849 m b\u7849 m v\u7915 a \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c: "Ch\u7881  c\'f3 b\'e0 b\'e0 l\'e0 ch\u7871 t gi\'e0, b\'e0 b\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i theo b\'e0 l\'e3o v\'e0o nh\'e0, b\'ean trong r\u7845 t t\u7889 i, c\u7917 a s\u7893  \u273 \u7873 u d\'e1n b\u7841 t nh\u7921 a \u273 en, b\u7841 t r\u7845 t d\'e0y l\'e0m \'e1nh s\'e1ng kh\'f4ng xuy\'ean qua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, m\u7863 t b\'e0 l\'e3o trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i tr\u7903  n\'ean tr\u7855 ng xanh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng kh\uc0\u7887 i n\u7855 m tay th\'e0nh quy\u7873 n, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u, ch\u7907 t tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y tr\'ean chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7845 p d\u7921 a v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kinh ng\u7841 c l\u7841 i c\u7843 m k\'edch m\'e0 nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'e0 l\'e3o: "B\'e0..."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ti\uc0\u7875 u nha \u273 \u7847 u gi\u7845 u ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean l\u7847 u, b\'e0 b\'e0 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y n\'ean \u273 \'e3 chuy\u7875 n ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y." B\'e0 l\'e3o nh\'ecn l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, "B\'e0 b\'e0 kh\'f4ng h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\'e0 b\'e0 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7913 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 nh\'ecn s\uc0\u7855 c tr\u7901 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i: "S\u7855 p so\'e1t na r\u7891 i, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y s\u7869  b\u7883  t\'ecm ra. Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  so\'e1t ra r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Hi\uc0\u7879 n t\u7841 i s\u7907  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo l\uc0\u7901 i b\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i nh\'ecn th\u7901 i gian, \u273 \'e3 n\u259 m gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac c\uc0\u7853 u mang th\u7913  kia r\u7901 i th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia l\'e0 m\u7897 t gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  nh\u7853 n ra \u273 \'e3 tr\'f4i qua th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 ch\uc0\u7881  v\u7873  ph\'eda mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na: "Thi\u7871 u ni\'ean v\'e0o trong mi\u7871 u tr\u7889 n \u273 i. Th\u7847 n Na s\u7869  c\u7913 u hai ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i v\uc0\u7853 y, gi\u7885 ng kh\'e0n kh\'e0n, bi\u7875 u l\u7897  tr\'ean m\u7863 t v\u7851 n c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901  kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m x\'fac, trong \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7909 c ng\u7847 u l\u7841 i to\'e1t ra v\u7867  bu\u7891 n b\'e3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i b\'e0, n\'f3i c\'e1m \u417 n xong chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ch\'e0o b\'e0 l\'e3o r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c khi \u273 i c\u7853 u nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7887 i: "B\'e0 \u417 i, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  so\'e1t ra kia nh\'ecn nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o \u7841 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e0 hai sai d\uc0\u7883 ch, t\u7899 i n\u417 i n\'e0y t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 y ch\'ednh l\'e0 hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7905  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 i ra c\u7917 a, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn b\'e0 l\'e3o, n\'f3i kh\u7869 : "Sao b\'e0 b\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u tin t\u432 \u7903 ng b\'e0 l\'e3o c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u \'fd c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o ch\uc0\u7881  l\'ean tr\u7901 i: "Kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, b\'e0 b\'e0 ch\u7871 t mu\u7897 n m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a. Ai c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7847 u tr\u7901 i \'e2m u x\'e1m x\u7883 t nh\u432  ch\'ec, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'e1i l\u7891 ng th\u7853 t l\u7899 n, bao tr\u7885 n c\u7843  th\'f4n \u7903  trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t s\u7899 m \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u x\u7917  l\'fd hai ti\u7875 u qu\u7927  kia, sau khi b\u7883  \u273 \u7889 t s\u7841 ch ch\'fang gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  kho\u7843 ng tr\u7901 i n\'e0y h\'fat v\'e0o. C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\u7889  \'fd d\'f9ng m\'e1u v\u7869  ph\'f9 v\'e3ng sinh l\'ean b\'fap b\'ea n\u7919  \u273 \u7891 ng kia, c\u361 ng v\'f4 d\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7905  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ra ngo\'e0i xong kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na tr\u7889 n nh\u432  l\u7901 i b\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i m\'e0 \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7893 ng th\'f4n l\u7845 y xe m\'e1y. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng tin mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na kia c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7913 u b\u7885 n h\u7885 , n\u7871 u qu\u7843  th\u7853 t c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7913 u, v\'ec sao l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0 l\'e3o kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia tr\u7889 n v\'e0o trong mi\u7871 u? N\u7871 u qu\u7843  th\u7853 t c\'f3 th\u7847 n linh, t\u7841 i sao l\u7841 i ng\u7891 i nh\'ecn th\'f4n tr\u7845 n m\'ecnh ph\'f9 h\u7897  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c tr\u7847 n gian?\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i v\uc0\u7853 y ch\u7859 ng qua ch\u7881  l\'e0 \'f4m hy v\u7885 ng v\'e0 ch\'fat ni\u7873 m tin cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\'e0o t\'edn ng\u432 \u7905 ng, kh\u7849 n c\u7847 u k\u7923  t\'edch xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n m\'e0 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec b\'e0 bi\u7871 t r\'f5 b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\u7901 i gian, ch\u7841 y kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n mu\u7889 n th\u7917 , d\u7877  d\'e0ng cam ch\u7883 u s\u7889  ph\u7853 n m\u7899 i l\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7901 ng t\u7915  ch\u7895  b\'e0 l\'e3o tr\u7903  l\u7841 i c\u7893 ng th\'f4n d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  k\'e9o d\'e0i v\'f4 t\u7853 n. Ho\u7863 c n\'f3i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\u7851 n d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u sau khi qua gi\u7919 a tr\u432 a, th\u7901 i gian ban ng\'e0y b\u7883  ng\u7855 n \u273 i d\u7847 n. R\'f5 r\'e0ng m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e0i, khi c\u7853 u \u273 \u7905  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7893 ng th\'f4n, s\u7855 c tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n bi\u7871 n \u273 en.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean di \uc0\u273 \u7897 ng hi\u7879 n th\u7901 i gian l\'e0 t\'e1m gi\u7901  t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'e2y th\uc0\u7915 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u273 \u7905  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u7889  \u273 \u7883 nh tr\'ean xe, l\'e1i xe t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  cao nh\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7841 y ra kh\u7887 i th\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i ch\u7915 ng m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat, con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u tr\u7903  n\'ean b\u7857 ng ph\u7859 ng r\u7897 ng r\'e3i \'97\'97 b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f9 d\uc0\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, l\'fac n\'e0y ph\'f9 d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  d\u7853 y n\u7893 i hi\u7879 u qu\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7847 m m\u7855 ng m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, l\u7841 i l\'e1i xe ra ngo\'e0i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, l\u7847 n n\'e0y ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 \u273 i theo h\u432 \u7899 ng *Sinh M\'f4n trong b\'e1t qu\'e1i, nh\u432 ng n\u7917 a gi\u7901  sau c\u7853 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y bi\u7875 n hi\u7879 u ti\u7879 m t\u7841 p h\'f3a quen thu\u7897 c \u7903  c\u7893 ng th\'f4n.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (Sinh m\'f4n l\'e0 m\uc0\u7897 t trong t\'e1m c\u7917 a g\u7891 m c\'f3 H\u432 u M\'f4n, Sinh M\'f4n, Th\u432 \u417 ng M\'f4n, \u272 \u7895  M\'f4n, C\u7843 nh M\'f4n, T\u7917  M\'f4n, Kinh M\'f4n v\'e0 Khai M\'f4n. T\'e1m c\u7917 a n\'e0y l\'e0 t\u7915  t\'e1m ph\u432 \u417 ng v\u7883  c\u7911 a B\'e1t Qu\'e1i m\'e0 ra. Sinh m\'f4n l\'e0 c\u7917 a s\u7889 ng duy nh\u7845 t trong t\'e1m c\u7917 a)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Hai gi\uc0\u7901  sau, \u273 \'e3 th\u7917  t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p c\'f3 th\u7875 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i \u7903  c\u7893 ng th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia. Xe m\'e1y \u273 \'e3 h\u7871 t x\u259 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong t\uc0\u7847 m m\u7855 t xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \'e1nh l\u7917 a tr\'f9ng \u273 i\u7879 p, c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng chi\'eang tr\u7889 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng. C\u259 ng m\u7855 t nh\'ecn qua, \u273 i \u273 \u7847 u l\'e0 m\u7897 t nh\'f3m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 eo na di\u7879 n, gi\u417  \u273 \'e8n l\u7891 ng gi\u7845 y th\u7855 p n\u7871 n, khua chi\'eang g\'f5 tr\u7889 ng, vung \u273 ao ki\u7871 m nh\u432  \u273 \u7841 o c\u7909  tr\'ean s\'e2n kh\u7845 u, r\u7847 m r\u7853 p \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7893 ng th\'f4n. M\'e0u s\u7855 c ki\u7875 u d\'e1ng m\u7863 t n\u7841  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'e1c nhau, c\'f3 nh\'edu m\'e0y tr\u7907 n m\u7855 t, c\'f3 m\u7863 t m\u361 i cong cong, c\'f3 ng\u7899  ng\u7849 n \u273 \u7847 n \u273 \u7897 n, d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh l\u7917 a chi\u7871 u l\'fac s\'e1ng l\'fac t\u7889 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  bi\u7871 t c\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i theo sau nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 o\'e0n th\'f4n d\'e2n v\'e2y quanh xem n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t, c\'f3 v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng ch\u7911  ti\u7879 m t\u7841 p h\'f3a \u7903  c\u7893 ng th\'f4n, c\'f3 m\u7897 t nh\'e0 ba ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7911  nh\'e0 tr\u7885 , c\'f2n c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng l\'fac t\'ecm hi\u7875 u tin t\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Theo m\'e0n \uc0\u273 \'eam ho\'e0n to\'e0n bu\'f4ng xu\u7889 ng, con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ra kh\u7887 i th\'f4n d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  b\u7883  \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 \u7873 u v\u7851 n \u273 \u7843 o quanh t\u7841 i ch\u7895 . Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \u273 i tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng g\'f5 g\'f5 \u273 \'e1nh \u273 \'e1nh gi\u417  \u273 ao m\'faa ki\u7871 m nh\'ecn c\'f3 v\u7867  \u273 i kh\'f4ng nhanh, k\'ec th\u7921 c r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n c\u7893 ng th\'f4n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7907  b\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh th\u7871  c\u7845 p b\'e1ch k\'e9o T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nhanh ch\'f3ng tr\u7889 n v\'e0o nh\'e0 kho ph\'eda sau ti\u7879 m t\u7841 p h\'f3a \u7903  c\u7893 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c sau nh\'e0 kho \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 c\u7917 a, c\u7917 a tr\u432 \u7899 c d\u7877  b\u7873  cho ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i v\'e0o chuy\u7875 n h\'e0ng h\'f3a l\'ean qu\u7847 y ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e1n, c\u7917 a sau n\u7889 i th\u7859 ng v\u7899 i s\'e2n sau, ti\u7879 n cho vi\u7879 c d\u7905  h\'e0ng t\u7915  tr\'ean xe xu\u7889 ng chuy\u7875 n th\u7859 ng v\'e0o kho.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a tr\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7917  m\u7903  c\u7917 a sau \'97\'97 c\'e1nh c\u7917 a kia kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 bao l\'e2u kh\'f4ng s\u7917  d\u7909 ng, \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n hoen g\u7881 , kh\'f4ng th\u7875  m\u7903  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n c\u7853 u k\'e9o \u273 \u7849 y nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\uc0\u7871 n s\u7855 c, nh\u7853 n ra th\u7871  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c g\'ec nh\u7889 t m\'ecnh v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\'e0o tuy\u7879 t c\u7843 nh, \u273 ang mu\u7889 n k\'e9o c\u7917 a tr\u432 \u7899 c ra tr\u7889 n \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  kh\'e1c th\'ec ch\u7907 t nghe th\u7845 y b\'ean ngo\'e0i \u7891 n \'e0o, to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \'e1m "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" kia \u273 \'e3 ch\u7863 n \u7903  c\u7917 a ra v\'e0o ti\u7879 m. T\u7915  trong khe c\u7917 a c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u7903  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a ni\u7879 m g\'ec \u273 \'f3, ngay sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 eo na di\u7879 n m\'e0u \u273 o\u777  c\u7847 m \u273 \'e8n l\u7891 ng d\u7851 n theo hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 eo na di\u7879 n kh\'e1c \u273 i v\'e0o, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ni\u7879 m ch\'fa, tra so\'e1t l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t t\u7915 ng ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  \u273 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 "So\'e1t na" nh\u432  l\u7901 i b\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i. \'d4ng ch\u7911  ti\u7879 m t\u7841 p h\'f3a c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng n\'f3i, nghi th\u7913 c n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  t\'ecm v\'e0 tr\u7909 c xu\u7845 t ma t\'e0 b\u7879 nh d\u7883 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kia r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 so\'e1t \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 kho, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 eo na di\u7879 n m\'e0u \u273 o\u777  \u273 \u7853 p \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a, h\'f4: "Sao c\u7917 a n\'e0y l\u7841 i kh\'f3a?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i c\'e0ng th\'eam lo l\u7855 ng, nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng b\'ean ngo\'e0i li\u7873 n c\'e0ng d\'f9ng s\u7913 c m\'e0 \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a sau r\u7881  s\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i c\uc0\u7917 a m\u7897 t gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7863 c kh\u7849 u \'e2m vang l\'ean: "\u272 \u7841 i b\'e1, b\'ean trong c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng, h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ng\u432 ng \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng "ng\u432 \u7901 i" ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a y\'ean t\u297 nh m\u7897 t gi\'e2y, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c vang l\'ean ti\u7871 ng kim lo\u7841 i va ch\u7841 m nh\u7913 c tai c\'f9ng v\u7899 i ti\u7871 ng ch\'eca kh\'f3a c\u7855 m v\'e0o \u7893 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c b\u7845 t ch\u7845 p t\u7845 t c\u7843 , d\u7891 n h\u7871 t s\u7913 c nh\u7845 c ch\'e2n \u273 \u7841 p l\'ean c\u7917 a sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 "R\uc0\u7847 m" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, hai c\u7917 a tr\u432 \u7899 c sau \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i m\u7903  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn l\u7841 i, c\'f5ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\'ean ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng ra ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'eda sau c\uc0\u7853 u lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng vang l\'ean gi\u7885 ng \u273 \u7883 a ph\u432 \u417 ng: "\u272 \u7841 i b\'e1, ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, li\u7879 u c\'f3 ph\u7843 i k\u7867  tr\u7897 m kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i tr\u7897 m, l\'e0... qu\u7927 . B\u7885 n ch\'fang kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\'f3ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng d\u7915 ng, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn l\u7841 i \'97\'97 nh\u7919 ng h\'ecnh b\'f3ng lay \u273 \u7897 ng d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh l\u7917 a, m\'ecnh v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\'f3ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tim c\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7843 y d\u7921 ng, nh\u432 ng gi\u7901  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  suy ngh\u297  qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u, ch\u7881  c\'f5ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m li\u7873 u m\u7841 ng ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c. C\u7893 ng th\'f4n kh\'f4ng ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 ch\u7841 y sang b\'ean kia th\'f4n, c\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 n\u417 i n\'e0y d\u7921 a v\'e0o s\u432 \u7901 n n\'fai, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7889 n v\'e0o trong n\'fai.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7851 n b\u7845 t t\u7881 nh th\u7871  n\'e0y tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng nhanh ch\'f3ng ch\u7841 y ra, cho d\'f9 kh\'f4ng b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia b\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng s\u7907  l\'e0 c\u361 ng s\u7855 p kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau l\uc0\u432 ng \'e1nh l\u7917 a c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7847 m \u273 \u7847 u mang na di\u7879 n m\'e0u \u273 o\u777  c\'e1ch c\u7853 u c\'f9ng l\u7855 m ch\u7881  m\u7845 y m\'e9t. C\u7843  \u273 o\'e0n d\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai t\u7909 t l\u7841 i, k\u7875  c\u7843  th\'f4n d\'e2n xem n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t c\u361 ng theo s\'e1t ph\'eda sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7841 y kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i, kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, trong l\'fac b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n ngo\'e0i mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\uc0\u7921 a ch\u7885 n n\'e0o kh\'e1c, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ch\u7841 y c\u361 ng s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kia \u273 u\u7893 i k\u7883 p, c\u7853 u x\u7889 c l\u7841 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, x\'f4 c\u7917 a m\u7903  ra, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i th\u7863 t ch\u7863 t, d\'f9ng m\'e1u m\'ecnh v\u7869  m\u7897 t t\u7845 m ph\'f9 phong c\u7845 m \u7903  ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong b\uc0\u7885 n ch\'fang c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 n\'f3i ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n v\u7851 n c\'f2n b\u7843 o l\u432 u \'fd th\u7913 c l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i, th\u7853 m ch\'ed ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng \'fd th\u7913 c r\u7857 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, cho n\'ean b\u7885 n ch\'fang trong th\u7901 i gian ng\u7855 n v\u7851 n ch\u432 a d\'e1m x\'f4ng t\u7899 i mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n. Ch\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n khi b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u x\'f4ng v\'e0o mi\u7871 u, mu\u7889 n ph\'e1 gi\u7843 i t\u7845 m ph\'f9 kia c\u361 ng v\u7851 n c\u7847 n ch\'fat th\u7901 i gian.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian m\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  tranh th\u7911  cho b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\'fac n\'e0y, d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong mi\uc0\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na c\'f3 \'e1nh l\u7917 a y\u7871 t \u7899 t, tr\u432 \u7899 c khi b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u nghi th\u7913 c so\'e1t na c\'f3 l\u7869  ch\'fang \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i mi\u7871 u tr\u432 \u7899 c, v\u7853 y n\'ean nhang n\u7871 n tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901  tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7863 t T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m d\u7921 a v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng, m\u432 \u7907 n \'e1nh l\u7917 a hiu h\u7855 t m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 khung c\u7843 nh b\u7889 n ph\'eda, suy ngh\u297  bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p c\'f3 th\u7875  tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i v\'e2y kh\u7889 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y c\uc0\u7853 u ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i n\u259 m chi\u7871 c na di\u7879 n g\u7847 n c\u7917 a nh\u7845 t tr\'ean t\u432 \u7901 ng. Ch\'fang nh\'ecn r\u7845 t m\u7899 i, m\'e0u s\u7855 c t\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7865 p, tr\'ean m\u7863 t n\u7841  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'edch nhi\u7873 u b\u7909 i b\u7863 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'fang \uc0\u273 \u7873 u \u273 ang c\u432 \u7901 i, m\u7863 t m\'e0y t\u432 \u417 i r\'f3i, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng trong l\'fac c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7867  m\u7863 t l\u7841 i tho\'e1ng to\'e1t ra s\u7921  s\u7907  h\'e3i v\'e0 s\u7847 u o\'e1n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba m\uc0\u7863 t n\u7841  ph\'eda tr\'ean m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng nh\u432  da ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 m\u7897 t nam m\u7897 t n\u7919  v\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9; hai m\u7863 t n\u7841  ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i m\'e0u \u273 \u7887 , b\u7889 n m\u7855 t tr\u7907 n l\'ean, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\u7921 c k\u7923  kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u h\'e0m ngh\u297 a m\'e0u s\u7855 c c\u7911 a na di\u7879 n trong qu\u7927  h\'ed, nh\u432 ng trong kinh k\u7883 ch, m\'e0u \u273 o\u777  t\u432 \u7907 ng tr\u432 ng cho l\'f2ng can \u273 \u7843 m trung th\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \u7845 y. Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m m\u7915 ng n\u259 m m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m nay \u273 \'e3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  so\'e1t ra qu\u7927 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f3 na di\uc0\u7879 n. Thu ph\u7909 c \'e1c qu\u7927  v\'e0o trong na di\u7879 n, \'e1c qu\u7927  b\u7883  phong \u7845 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\'fa \uc0\u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y \u273 i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng b\u7883  b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\u7855 t \u273 i s\u7869  b\u7883  l\'e0m th\'e0nh na di\u7879 n \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "..."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i n\'f3i c\u7911 a \'f4ng ch\u7911  ti\u7879 m t\u7841 p h\'f3a v\'e0 O\'e1nh O\'e1nh \u273 an xen trong \u273 \u7847 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong l\'f2ng ph\'e1t l\u7841 nh, nh\'ecn qua n\u259 m chi\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841  kia, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y nh\'e0 Chu Huy \uc0\u273 i ra ngo\'e0i l\'e0 m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m th\'e1ng gi\'eang, trong th\'f4n ch\u7855 c h\u7859 n c\u361 ng th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n nghi l\u7877  nh\u7843 y na v\'e0 so\'e1t na nh\u432  h\'f4m nay, \'e1nh l\u7917 a chi\u7871 u tr\u7901 i, khua chi\'eang g\'f5 tr\u7889 ng, ba ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t nh\'e0 \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ch\u7895  ng\'e3 ba c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t d\u7877  d\'e0ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a th\'f4n. B\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i b\u7897  v\'e0o th\'f4n xin gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , l\u7841 i b\u7883  th\'f4n d\'e2n cho l\'e0 ma qu\u7927  b\u7855 t h\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai c\uc0\u7843 nh s\'e1t truy t\'ecm tung t\'edch nh\'e0 Chu Huy \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e0 b\'e0 gi\u7845 u v\'e0o trong nh\'e0 m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  b\u7855 t ra trong l\'fac so\'e1t na.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  cho r\u7857 ngm\'ecnh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, coi ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e0nh qu\u7927  b\u7855 t l\u7841 i h\'e0nh quy\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a chuy\u7875 n \'e1nh m\u7855 t v\u7873  ph\'eda t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i do \u7843 o gi\'e1c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u hay kh\'f4ng, d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n chi\u7871 u r\u7885 i, t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n kia v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 to l\u7899 n s\u7915 ng s\u7919 ng, v\u7851 n \u273 eo m\u7863 t n\u7841  m\'e0u v\'e0ng \u273 en, m\u7863 c \'e1o b\'e0o g\u7845 m m\'e0u \u273 o\u777  nh\u432  \'e1o b\'e0o trong kinh k\u7883 ch, nh\u432 ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 v\u7867  cao h\u417 n r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7917  th\u7847 n Na Th\'e1i T\u7917  c\u7853 u th\u7845 y l\'fac s\'e1ng. Kh\'f4ng h\u7873  gi\u7889 ng ti\u7875 u h\'e0i t\u7917  b\u7883  m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7899 n m\'e0 gi\u7889 ng th\'e2n h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n, nh\'edu nh\'edu m\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m ma qu\u7927  t\u7871  b\'e1i, s\u7869  l\'e0 th\u7847 n g\'ec \u273 \'e2y; nh\'ecn \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng nh\'e2n gian \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c \u273 \u7843 o \u273 i\'ean, s\u7869  th\u7847 n g\'ec \u273 \'e2y. Ho\u7863 c c\u259 n b\u7843 n v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe th\u7845 y m\u7897 t \'e2m thanh c\u7921 c k\'ec tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p: "Ng\u432 \u417 i mu\u7889 n c\u7847 u ta c\u7913 u ng\u432 \u417 i v\'e0 b\u7841 n ng\u432 \u417 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c n\'f3i, n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t n\u7917 a m\u7899 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p, kinh h\'e3i m\'e0 nh\'ecn xung quanh, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng y\'ean l\u7863 ng, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901 \'97\'97 v\u7915 a r\u7891 i, l\'e0 t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432  \u273 \u7875  nghi\u7879 m ch\u7913 ng ph\u7887 ng \u273 o\'e1n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, thanh \'e2m kia l\u7841 i vang l\'ean: "Ng\u432 \u417 i mu\u7889 n c\u7847 u ta c\u7913 u ng\u432 \u417 i v\'e0 b\u7841 n ng\u432 \u417 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n, thanh \'e2m th\u7853 t s\u7921  ph\'e1t ra t\u7915  t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nu\uc0\u7889 t nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng thu h\u7891 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  \'fd ngh\u297  b\u7845 t k\'ednh v\u7915 a r\u7891 i trong \u273 \u7847 u, nh\u432 ng t\'e2m v\u7851 n c\'f3 nghi k\u7883  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean "Hi\u7875 n linh" n\'e0y. Tr\'ean th\u7871  gian th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7847 n sao? Hay l\'e0 n\'f3i, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i ma qu\u7927 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ma qu\u7927  n\'e0y t\u432  duy h\u417 i kh\'e1c? Th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7889  \'fd l\u7915 a c\u7853 u m\u7855 c c\'e2u?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t tr\'ean \u273 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7919 a c\u417 m mi\u7877 n ph\'ed, c\'f3 l\'e0 th\u7847 n linh th\'ec c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n nh\'e2n gian cung ph\u7909 ng, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 th\u7847 n hay qu\u7927 , ch\u7881  c\u7847 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\'fap c\u7853 u v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i kh\u7889 n c\u7843 nh, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'e2n nh\u7855 c giao d\u7883 ch v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. D\'f9 sao c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 qu\u7927  b\'e0 b\'e0 s\u7861 n l\'f2ng gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7845 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng, c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o gi\u7845 u gi\u7871 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'fang, t\'f4i mu\u7889 n c\u7847 u ng\'e0i c\u7913 u ch\'fang t\'f4i. Ch\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\u7871 u mu\u7889 n c\u7847 u ng\'e0i c\u7913 u th\'ec ch\'fang t\'f4i ph\u7843 i tr\u7843  l\u7841 i g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Lo\uc0\u7841 i \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n n\'e0y t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'e0 n\'ean n\'f3i r\'f5 r\'e0ng tr\u432 \u7899 c. D\'f9 l\'e0 th\u7847 n th\u7853 t th\'ec c\u361 ng c\'f3 \'e1c th\u7847 n. N\'f3i tr\u7855 ng ra l\'e0, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 n\'f3i, th\u7847 n v\'e0 qu\u7927  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 t kia nghe n\'f3i v\u7853 y l\u7841 i kh\u7869  n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i: "Ng\u432 \u417 i h\u7887 i ta mu\u7889 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n c\u7911 a ta r\u7845 t \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, ng\u432 \u417 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 i t\u7899 i, h\'f4n ta, l\'e0 \u273 \u7911  r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
