\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i. C\u7853 u ch\u7847 n ch\u7915  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda chi\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841  v\'e0u v\'e0ng \u273 en kia, d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n ch\u7853 p ch\u7901 n, n\'e9t m\u7863 t khi c\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a m\u7863 t n\u7841  c\'e0ng t\u259 ng th\'eam m\u7845 y ph\u7847 n t\'e0 d\u7883 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng l\u7847 n n\u7919 a, kh\'e0n kh\'e0n tr\u7847 m tr\u7847 m, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\'f2 t\u7915  d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c l\'ean \u273 \'f2i l\u7845 y n\u7909  h\'f4n n\'e0y: "Nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o? Kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u7841  m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng, nh\'ecn qua nhang n\u7871 n tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901 : "T\'f4i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i trong l\'f2ng r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t th\u7847 n linh trong mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na n\'e0y t\u7841 i sao l\u7841 i \u273 \'f2i m\u7897 t y\'eau c\u7847 u k\'ec qu\'e1i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, trong \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 c\u7845 t gi\u7845 u th\'e2m \'fd v\u7899 i huy\u7873 n c\u417  g\'ec hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  bi\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 kh\u417 i d\u7853 y bao nhi\'eau t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n c\'f9ng kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng trong n\u7897 i t\'e2m ch\u7911  nh\'e2n thanh \'e2m kia, trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t th\u7853 m ch\'ed mu\u7889 n ph\'e1 n\'e1t mi\u7871 u th\u7901  r\'e1ch n\'e1t nh\u7887  b\'e9 n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 o b\u7889 i m\'ecnh ch\'e2n th\'e0nh b\u7843 o v\u7879  h\u417 n m\u432 \u7901 i n\u259 m, \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean \u273 \u7847 u tim c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng \u7903  trong t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i l\u7841 i th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh th\'edch? M\u7897 t tia h\u7891 n ph\'e1ch c\u7911 a h\u7855 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\'e1m b\'ean c\u7853 u, v\u7853 y m\'e0 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hay ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra ch\'fat manh m\u7889 i n\'e0o. H\u7855 n c\'f2n lu\'f4n cho r\u7857 ng A Di\'ean ng\u7889 c, kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed th\u7847 m ngh\u297  ng\u7889 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, chung quy h\u7855 n s\u7869  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7841 y c\u7853 u th\'f4ng su\u7889 t, d\u7841 y c\u7853 u hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c y\'eau, nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\u7845 t c\u7843  nhu t\'ecnh m\u7853 t \'fd c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  l\'e0 c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kia l\'e0 ai. L\'e0 n\u7919  sinh ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh t\u432 \u417 i s\'e1ng vui v\u7867  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'edch trong tr\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u? A Di\'ean kh\'f4ng hay nh\'ecn c\'f4 ta kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c, m\'e0 l\'e0 v\'ec x\u7845 u h\u7893 ? Hay l\'e0 t\'ean ng\u7889 c \u273 \'e3 c\u432 \u7899 i v\u7907  l\u7853 p gia \u273 \'ecnh, lu\'f4n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c A Di\'ean che ch\u7903  b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i kia? A Di\'ean kh\'f4ng coi t\'ean \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 huynh \u273 \u7879 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Chung quy kh\'f4ng c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau kh\uc0\u7843  n\u259 ng l\'e0 m\'ecnh, n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 khi g\u7863 p A Di\'ean b\u7843 n th\'e2n h\u7855 n m\u7899 i m\u432 \u7901 i b\u7889 n tu\u7893 i, mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7885 i l\'e0 thi\u7871 u ni\'ean, nh\u432 ng A Di\'ean khi \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i ch\'edn tu\u7893 i, ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887 ; th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i m\'ecnh A Di\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u7881  m\u7899 i m\u432 \u7901 i s\'e1u tu\u7893 i r\u432 \u7905 i. M\u7863 c d\'f9 n\'f3i h\'e0i t\u7917  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7873 u tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh s\u7899 m bi\u7871 t nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n, m\u432 \u7901 i b\u7889 n m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m tu\u7893 i l\'ean trung h\u7885 c \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t gi\u7845 u th\u7847 y c\'f4 gi\u7845 u ph\u7909  huynh y\'eau s\u7899 m, nh\u432 ng A Di\'ean nh\'e0 h\u7855 n l\u7841 i ng\u7889 c h\u417 n ch\'fat so v\u7899 i h\'e0i t\u7917  nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta, ng\u7889 c \u273 \u7871 n \u273 au l\'f2ng h\u7855 n, h\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\u7915 ng gi\'e2y t\u7915 ng ph\'fat che ch\u7903  trong ng\u7921 c, s\u7907  l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n khi qua \u273 \u7901 i A Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n coi h\u7855 n l\'e0 ca ca.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 su\uc0\u7889 t hai n\u259 m ni\'ean thi\u7871 u th\u7901 i thanh xu\'e2n t\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7865 p nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tham d\u7921  c\'f9ng; sau \u273 \'f3 khi h\u7855 n lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean c\u7853 u, h\u7857 ng \u273 \'eam \'f4m c\u7853 u, d\u7895  c\u7853 u ng\u7911 , l\'e9n h\'f4n c\u7853 u, A Di\'ean ng\u7889 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  n\'ean cho d\'f9 A Di\'ean nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i mu\u7889 n r\u7869  sang h\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'e1c, th\'edch ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'ean tr\'e1ch c\u7853 u, t\u7915  t\u7915  mang c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873  b\'ean m\'ecnh l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y h\u7855 n d\u7847 n kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c t\'e2m t\'ecnh, ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\u7851 n c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng: "Ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u432 \u417 i th\'edch quan tr\u7885 ng \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y? C\'f3 th\u7875  v\'ec h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n h\'f4n ta, th\u7853 m ch\'ed ngay c\u7843  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i v\'e0 b\u7841 n ng\u432 \u417 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn v\uc0\u7873  ph\'eda T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 ang d\u7921 a \u7903  t\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean kia h\'f4n m\'ea b\u7845 t t\u7881 nh, tr\'ean m\u7863 t l\u7897  ra ch\'fat do d\u7921 . N\u7871 u qu\u7843  th\u7853 t ch\u7881  m\u7897 t c\'e1i h\'f4n c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7893 i l\u7845 y c\u417  h\u7897 i cho hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7853 u s\u7869  ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o th\u7911  m\'e0 c\u7889  ch\u7845 p \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 , b\'ean n\'e0o n\u7863 ng b\'ean n\'e0o nh\u7865  c\u7853 u ph\'e2n r\u7845 t r\'f5. Hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m th\u7915 a d\u7883 p kh\'f4ng ai ch\'fa \'fd m\'e0 h\'f4n ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, m\u7845 t m\u7841 ng \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7863 p l\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, c\u7853 u m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i h\'f4n th\u7853 t s\u7921  qu\'e1 \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n m\'e0 k\u7923  l\u7841  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f3 tin, c\u7853 u s\u7907  ph\'eda sau c\'f3 b\u7851 y c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, m\u7899 i l\u7847 n l\u7919 a tr\'ec ho\'e3n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng th\'ec ngay b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng xem tr\u7885 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, h\u7855 n l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  n\u7893 i ghen t\u7925  v\'e0 t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, c\'f3 l\u7869  ta c\u361 ng n\'ean cho ng\u432 \u417 i th\u7845 y b\'ean ngo\'e0i gi\u7901  \u273 ang nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y hai m\u7855 t ch\u7907 t l\u7841 nh, c\u7853 u v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, l\'fac m\u7903  ra \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn xuy\'ean qua hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a mi\u7871 u th\u7845 y r\'f5 t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" kia \u273 ang bao v\'e2y b\'ean ngo\'e0i, nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7851 n \u273 \u7847 u \u273 eo na di\u7879 n gi\u417  \u273 \'e8n l\u7891 ng \u273 \u7913 ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\'e1c th\'f4n d\'e2n c\'f2n l\u7841 i x\'fam \u7903  ph\'eda sau. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7845 y \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t kh\'e1c l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c \'96 trong \u273 \'e8n l\u7891 ng gi\u7845 y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 \'e1nh l\u7917 a m\'e0u cam m\'e0 l\'e0 qu\u7927  h\u7887 a m\'e0u xanh, qu\u7927  h\u7887 a chi\u7871 u r\u7885 i, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7855 ng nh\u432  gi\u7845 y, bi\u7875 u l\u7897  c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901  v\'f4 h\u7891 n, kh\'f4ng \'e2n c\u7847 n hi\u7873 n h\'f2a nh\u432  ban ng\'e0y \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn qua m\uc0\u7897 t v\'f2ng, kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t ai l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\'f3 m\u7845 y khu\'f4n m\u7863 t d\u7919  t\u7907 n \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 , hi\u7879 n ra t\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7879  qu\u7927 , ch\u7913 ng minh r\'f5 b\u7885 n ch\'fang \u273 \'e3 h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i. C\'f4 b\'e9 O\'e1nh O\'e1nh, nh\'f3m nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7851 n \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7843 y na \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7859 ng tr\'e1ch c\u7853 u v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh l\u7917 a kia kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\'f3ng. B\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, d\u432 \u7899 i qu\u7927  h\u7887 a \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\'f3ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nghe n\'f3i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7901 i sinh c\'f3 m\u7855 t \'c2m D\u432 \u417 ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 nh\'ecn ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t v\u7853 t thu\u7897 c v\u7873  \'e2m hay d\u432 \u417 ng, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'f3 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c \u273 \'f3. Nh\u432 ng c\'f3 v\'e0i thu\u7853 t Th\'f4ng Linh c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng qu\u7927  qu\'e1i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p n\'e0y v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn l\'ean tr\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7847 u tr\u7901 i \'e2m u, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7843 nh \u273 \'eam trong tr\u7867 o m\'e0 l\'e0 s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 m\'e0u \u273 en m\'e0u x\'e1m \u273 an xen v\u7845 n v\'edt, quanh qu\u7849 n v\'f2ng \u273 i v\'f2ng l\u7841 i, l\u432 \u7907 n l\u7901  kh\'f4ng d\u7913 t \'97\'97 \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng qu\u7927  kh\'ed c\u7921 c k\u7923  d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c, to\'e0n b\u7897  th\'f4n \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  t\u7847 ng qu\u7927  kh\'ed n\'e0y bao ph\u7911 . Ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0 qu\u7927 , \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tr\'e1i tim b\u7883  b\'f3p ch\u7863 t. Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m g\u7885 i cho \u273 \u7891 ng s\u7921  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng h\u7873  nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i b\u7845 t k\'ec d\u7883  tr\u7841 ng g\'ec, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t trong th\'f4n \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, ng\u432 \u7901 i trong th\'f4n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t xung quanh m\'ecnh \u273 ang x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t \'e1c qu\u7927  l\u7867 n v\'e0o khi n\'e0o, ban \u273 \u7847 u c\'f3 l\u7869  ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t h\'f3a th\'e0nh \'e1c qu\u7927 , r\u7891 i sau \u273 \'f3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i xung quanh. B\u7903 i v\'ec \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7911 a qu\u7927  kh\'ed, ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903  b\'ean m\'ecnh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i hay qu\u7927 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed sau khi b\u7883  h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t c\u361 ng s\u7869  qu\'ean \u273 i k\'fd \u7913 c m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c s\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng. Qu\u7927  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 m\'ecnh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i hay qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ma qu\uc0\u7927  Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p \u7903  trong th\'f4n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 c\'f4 b\'e9 O\'e1nh O\'e1nh v\'e0 b\'e0 l\'e3o kia bi\u7871 t r\'f5 r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0 l\'e3o n\'f3i ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 m\'ecnh l\'e0 ch\u7871 t gi\'e0. Nh\u432  v\u7853 y nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u417  ng\'e1c \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, nh\'ecn \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c nh\'e2n gian ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a. \u272 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nghe th\u7845 y \'e2m thanh l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng h\u7887 i: "Nh\'ecn r\'f5 r\'e0ng r\u7891 i? Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\'e2u tr\u7843  l\u7901 i c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i l\'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\'ec sao ng\'e0i nh\uc0\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh mu\u7889 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i h\'f4n?" C\u7853 u h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c2m thanh kia t\uc0\u7921 a h\u7891  tr\u7847 m ng\'e2m ph\'fat ch\u7889 c, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i: "N\u417 i \u273 \'e2y qu\'e1 l\u7841 nh, mu\u7889 n ng\u432 \u417 i l\'e0m \u7845 m cho ta. Kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda \'e1nh n\u7871 n soi r\u7885 i t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901  l\'fac s\'e1ng l\'fac t\u7889 i, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "Ta mu\u7889 n th\u7881 nh ng\'e0i cam \u273 oan, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  m\u7897 t c\'e1i h\'f4n, vi\u7879 c g\'ec kh\'e1c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m. M\u7897 t c\'e1i h\'f4n, \u273 \u7893 i l\u7841 i t\'f4i v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m an to\'e0n nguy\'ean v\u7865 n ra kh\u7887 i th\'f4n n\'e0y. T\'f4i mu\u7889 n c\u7847 u ng\'e0i d\'f9ng t\u7909 c danh c\u7911 a ng\'e0i cam \u273 oan, \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 \u7841 t th\'e0nh, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7893 i \'fd."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1ch ra \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n r\u7891 i. \'c2m thanh kia n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i: "Ta kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'ean, nh\u432 ng ta c\'f3 th\u7875  cam \u273 oan \u273 \u432 a c\'e1c ng\u432 \u417 i an to\'e0n nguy\'ean v\u7865 n r\u7901 i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7913  cho t\'f4i n\'f3i th\u7859 ng." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, "Nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\'f4i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tin ng\'e0i." Thi\'ean \u273 \u7883 a v\u7841 n v\u7853 t, d\'f9 l\'e0 qu\u7927  th\u7847 n c\u361 ng c\'f3 t\'ean h\'fay, c\'f3 thi\'eang t\u7913 c c\'f3 danh. D\'f9ng t\'ean t\u7841 o \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  khi\u7871 n l\u7901 i th\u7873  c\'f3 hi\u7879 u l\u7921 c, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7893 i \'fd, vi ph\u7841 m \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh, t\'e2m kh\'f4ng th\'e0nh th\u7853 t d\'f9ng t\'ean gi\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  b\u7883  l\u7901 i th\u7873  ph\u7843 n ph\u7879 , l\u7853 p l\u7901 i th\u7873  c\'e0ng n\u7863 ng, ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  s\u7869  c\'e0ng m\u7841 nh. Th\u7913  n\'e0y l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  t\'ean h\'fay c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i l\'e0m Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng th\'eam ng\u7901  v\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng tin ta?" \'c2m thanh kia d\u7915 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean ta c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n l\u7901 i h\u7913 a. Ta s\u7869  \u273 u\u7893 i nh\u7919 ng k\u7867  b\'ean ngo\'e0i kia \u273 i, sau \u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u417 i t\u7899 i h\'f4n ta, ta s\u7869  cho c\'e1c ng\u432 \u417 i ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ta kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n kia c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u417 i. Nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u nh\u432  ng\u432 \u417 i kh\'f4ng th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n l\u7901 i h\u7913 a, v\u7853 y ng\u432 \u417 i ph\u7843 i \u273 em ch\'ednh ng\u432 \u417 i b\u7891 i th\u432 \u7901 ng ta, \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh ta kh\'f4ng bao gi\u7901  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7901 i \u273 i n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c." Suy ngh\u297  th\u7853 t l\'e2u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7865  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hi\uc0\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n kh\'e1c, n\u7871 u nh\u432  th\u7913  kia th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 u\u7893 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ra mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n, c\u7843  hai c\u361 ng s\u7869  ch\u7881  c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7871 t. M\'e0 gi\u7901  c\u7853 u c\'f2n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t nh\'e2n v\u7853 t \u273 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i m\'ecnh r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 th\u7847 n th\'e1nh ph\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0o, c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau b\u7843 n l\u297 nh.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Theo c\uc0\u7853 u g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u x\'e1c nh\u7853 n, hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a g\u7895  n\u7863 ng n\u7873  m\'e0u \u273 en b\u7895 ng nhi\'ean m\u7903  r\u7897 ng h\u432 \u7899 ng ra ngo\'e0i, y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i canh \u7903  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a v\'e0 c\u7843  Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i to\'e0n b\u7897  s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 \uc0\u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y b\u7847 u tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean bi\u7871 n \u273 \u7897 ng, d\'f2ng kh\'ed \u273 en quanh qu\u7849 n gi\u259 ng k\'edn tr\u7901 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u v\u7863 n v\u7865 o, xo\u7855 n l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay kh\u7893 ng l\u7891  l\'f4i k\'e9o, x\'e9 r\'e1ch, qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c2m phong th\uc0\u7893 i ng\u432 \u7907 c, nhang n\u7871 n tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901  nh\'e1y m\u7855 t b\u7883  th\u7893 i t\u7855 t, m\'e0n g\u7845 m tr\'ean x\'e0 nh\'e0 d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  trang tr\'ed b\u7883  th\u7893 i tung ph\u7847 n ph\u7853 t, r\u417 i t\'e1n lo\u7841 n tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t. Nh\u7919 ng "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" \u273 \u7913 ng ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u7883 u \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u \'f4m \u273 \u7847 u ng\'e3 tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t l\u259 n l\u7897 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  kh\'ed tr\'ean tr\u7901 i c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng m\u7887 ng, tr\u7901 i \u273 \'eam d\u7847 n hi\u7879 n ra khung c\u7843 nh v\u7889 n c\'f3. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u432 ng th\u7847 n nh\'ecn l\u7841 i, qu\u7927  kh\'ed gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  m\u7897 t lu\u7891 ng c\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7921 c h\'fat v\'e0o trong mi\u7871 u... Nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 trong mi\u7871 u l\'f4i ch\'fang, thu h\u7871 t v\'e0o trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong khung c\uc0\u7843 nh g\'e0o kh\'f3c h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y d\u432 \u7899 i m\'e1i hi\'ean \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n mi\u7871 u c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7845 p b\'e9 \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng, khi \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n c\u7853 u li\u7873 n kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u c\u432 \u7901 i, v\u7851 y v\u7851 y tay, ngay sau \u273 \'f3 b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i m\u7901  nh\u7841 t, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u n\u7919 a. L\'e0 b\'e0 l\'e3o \u273 \'e3 gi\'fap h\u7885  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i qu\u7927  kh\'ed phong b\u7871  th\'f4n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7843 i tr\u7915 , theo \u273 \'f3 b\'e0 c\u361 ng v\'e3ng sinh.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (v\'e3ng sinh: \uc0\u273 i \u273 \u7847 u thai)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y thanh \'e2m kia th\u7843 n nhi\'ean n\'f3i: "Nh\u7919 ng 'Ng\u432 \u7901 i" tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t kia \u273 ang nh\u7899  l\u7841 i n\u7895 i s\u7907  h\'e3i v\'e0 \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n khi ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, \u273 \u7907 i ch\'fang ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n s\u7921  th\u7853 t m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i c\u361 ng s\u7869  v\'e3ng sinh."\cb1 \
\cb3 Oan qu\uc0\u7927  v\'e0o lu\'e2n h\u7891 i, \'e1c qu\u7927  h\'f3a b\u7897 t m\u7883 n. Th\'f4n nh\u7887  n\'e0y, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng s\u7869  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh t\u7917  th\'f4n tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng, kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, tr\u7903  v\u7873  b\u7897  d\u7841 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u7913 ng v\u7899 i n\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u259 m chi\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841 , bi\u7875 u l\u7897  c\u7911 a ch\'fang c\u361 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  v\u7867  y\'ean b\'ecnh, m\u7863 t m\'e0y vui v\u7867 , kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng h\u432 \u7899 ng l\'ean, ch\u7881  l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng chi\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng \u273 \'fang th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y \'e2m thanh kia vang l\'ean, kh\'e0n kh\'e0n, tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p, l\u7841 i mang m\u7897 t ch\'fat \'f4n nhu quy\u7871 n luy\u7871 n: "\u272 \u7871 n l\'fac n\'ean ng\u432 \u417 i th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n \u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7883 nh r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i b\'ecnh t\u297 nh nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n kia. C\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng thay \u273 \u7893 i tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7845 t, trong ch\u7899 p m\u7855 t ti\'eau tr\u7915  qu\u7927  kh\'ed d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p o\'e1n kh\'ed nh\u432  th\u7871 , c\u7853 u tin \u273 \'e2y th\u7921 c s\u7921  l\'e0 th\u7847 n linh m\u7897 t ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0...\cb1 \
\cb3 Y\uc0\u7871 t h\u7847 u c\u7853 u gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t, t\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n th\u7901 , ng\u7849 ng m\u7863 t l\'ean, nh\'ecn chi\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841  m\'e0u v\'e0ng \u273 en kia, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u7871  ph\u7849 m ch\u7901  b\u7883  hi\u7871 n t\u7871  cho th\u7847 n linh: "Ng\'e0i c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c v\'ec sao... v\'ec sao l\u7841 i ng\u7891 i y\'ean kh\'f4ng qu\u7843 n?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 h\u7887 i. R\'f5 r\'e0ng l\'e0 th\u7847 n linh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng trong mi\u7871 u, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'ean che ch\u7903  sinh linh n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y? V\'ec sao tr\u432 \u7899 c kia ch\u7881  ng\u7891 i nh\'ecn b\u7885 n h\u7885  h\'f3a th\'e0nh o\'e1n qu\u7927  gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y, ch\u7871 t l\u7863 ng s\u7889 ng qua ng\'e0y, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  si\'eau sinh?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c2m thanh kia ch\uc0\u7881  th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng c\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i ta che ch\u7903  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u417 i n\'e0y, ta ch\u7881  che ch\u7903  em. A Di\'ean ng\u7889 c. Ta l\'e0 theo ch\'e2n em m\'e0 t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'eda sau chi\uc0\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841 , ng\u7909 y th\u7847 n s\u7855 c m\u7863 t nhu h\'f2a, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7899 i b\'e0n th\u7901  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai c\'e1nh c\uc0\u7917 a m\'e0u \u273 en l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a im \u7855 ng \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i, nhang \u273 \'e8n m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  l\u7841 i ch\u7853 p ch\u7901 n s\'e1ng l\'ean, ph\'e1t ra \'e1nh s\'e1ng \u7845 m \'e1p l\u7901  m\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n \u7903  tr\'ean cao, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng v\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7871 n h\u7855 n, v\'ec v\u7853 y do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i tr\'e8o l\'ean tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901 , t\u7915  t\u7915  s\'e1t l\u7841 i g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e0ng l\uc0\u7841 i g\u7847 n, m\u7863 t n\u7841  m\'e0u v\'e0ng \u273 en c\'f9ng \'e1o b\'e0o g\u7845 m m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  ph\u7911  tr\'ean t\u432 \u7907 ng c\'e0ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y r\'f5. Trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i sinh ra \u7843 o gi\'e1c, ph\'eda sau chi\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841  v\'e0 \'e1o cho\'e0ng n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7853 t, l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\u417  th\u7875  s\u7889 ng s\u7901  s\u7901  m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\u432 \u417 \u803 ng th\u226 \u768 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7841 c t\u7915  g\u7895  hay n\u7863 n t\u7915  \u273 \u7845 t s\'e9t.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t c\u7853 u c\'e1ch chi\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841  c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thanh \'e2m tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p: "Nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c nghe l\u7901 i m\'e0 nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, h\'f4n l\'ean chi\u7871 c m\u7863 t n\u7841  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 sinh kh\'ed kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \u7891  v\u7853 t l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o \u432 \u7899 t \'e1t c\u7841 y m\u7903  m\'f4i c\u7853 u, d\'f2 x\'e9t \u273 i v\'e0o, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng tr\'eau ch\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7847 u ch\u432 a k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, thu\u7853 n theo m\'e0 ng\u7891 i qu\u7923  \u7903  \u273 \'f3, ng\u7917 a \u273 \u7847 u h\u417 i h\'e9 m\'f4i m\u7863 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0m. \u272 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  kia \u273 ang l\'e0m g\'ec l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7843  kinh, \u273 ang mu\u7889 n m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra, nh\u432 ng c\'f2n ch\u432 a k\u7883 p m\u7903  \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n \'e2m phong k\'e9o t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\u7883  th\u7913  kia \u273 \u7849 y ng\'e3 tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871  n\u7871 n r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a lay l\u7855 t m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i d\u7853 p t\u7855 t. Mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n l\u7841 i ch\'ecm v\'e0o trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  m\u7855 t, v\u432 \u417 n tay ngh\u7865 n c\u7893  gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a \u273 \u7849 y ra, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\'fa con b\u7883  th\u7907  s\u259 n b\u7855 t trong tay t\'f9y \'fd ng\u7855 m ngh\'eda l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\u7889 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u d\u7847 n th\'edch \u7913 ng v\u7899 i b\'f3ng t\u7889 i, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y h\'ecnh d\'e1ng x\'e0 nh\'e0 tr\'ean n\'f3c, c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y t\u7915 ng chi\u7871 c na di\u7879 n tr\'ean t\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean ph\u7843 i nh\'ecn gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y g\'ec tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c, c\u7853 u c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 ang du t\u7849 u m\'fat l\u7845 y trong mi\u7879 ng m\'ecnh, c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e0n tay l\u7841 nh bu\u7889 t t\u7915  d\u432 \u7899 i v\u7841 t \'e1o \u273 i v\'e0o kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng vu\u7889 t ve \u273 \'f9a b\u7905 n, c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7913 c n\u7863 ng \'e1p \u7903  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c g\'ec m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a tr\u7885 ng l\u7921 c, b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c tr\u432 \u7907 t t\u7915  ng\u7921 c xu\u7889 ng c\u7893  c\u7853 u. Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec sao, b\'ecnh s\u7913  lu\'f4n c\u7913 u c\u7853 u trong l\'fac nguy nan l\u7847 n n\'e0y l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, c\'f3 l\u7869  b\u7903 i v\'ec th\u7913  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t qu\'e1 m\u7841 nh, d\'f9 l\'e0 b\'ecnh s\u7913  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'ecnh s\u7913  tr\u417 n b\'f3ng, t\u7913  chi v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  n\'ean v\'f4 l\u7921 c \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\u7841 i c\'f3 s\u7913 c, c\u7853 u d\u7891 n s\u7913 c \u273 \u7849 y m\u7897 t c\'e1i, \u273 \u7849 y th\u7913  kia t\u7915  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng ch\u7889 ng m\u7863 t b\'e0n b\'f2 d\u7853 y, nh\'ecn v\'e0o h\u432  kh\'f4ng n\'f3i: "... Ng\'e0i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i h\'f4n xong s\u7869  \u273 \u432 a ch\'fang t\'f4i an to\'e0n ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ng\'e0i n\'ean th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n l\u7901 i h\u7913 a r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai m\uc0\u7855 t c\u7853 u m\u7903  l\u7899 n, \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7917  m\'e0u \u273 en ph\'e1t s\'e1ng, nh\u432  s\u432  t\u7917  con b\u7883  ch\u7885 c gi\u7853 n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e0m g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thanh \'e2m kia l\uc0\u7841 nh nh\u7841 t n\'f3i: "C\'e1c ng\u432 \u417 i \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n s\'e1ng mai, b\u7841 n ng\u432 \u417 i t\u7921  nhi\'ean s\u7869  t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 c\'e1c ng\u432 \u417 i t\u7921  r\u7901 i \u273 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'f5 r\'e0ng \uc0\u273 \'e3 n\'f3i s\u7869  \u273 \u432 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i, b\u7903 i v\'ec m\'ecnh \u273 \u7849 y ra n\'ean c\'e1u k\u7881 nh r\u7891 i? Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7847 m ngh\u297  trong b\u7909 ng nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \'fd ki\u7871 n th\'eam. Th\'f4n \u273 \'e3 y\'ean \u7893 n tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0 t\u297 nh m\u7883 ch, sau khi tr\u7901 i s\'e1ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7921  \u273 i c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 sao ba ti\uc0\u7871 ng n\u7919 a l\'e0 tr\u7901 i s\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nghe ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  v\'e0 \u273 \'e8 n\'e9n ph\'eda sau thanh \'e2m kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Ng\'e0y qua ng\'e0y nh\'ecn ng\u7855 m c\u7853 u, \'f4m c\u7853 u, th\u7915 a d\u7883 p c\u7853 u ng\u7911  m\'e0 l\'e9n h\'f4n \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7887 a m\'e3n h\u7855 n. H\u7855 n kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 mu\u7889 n c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng kh\'f4ng sao. B\u7885 n h\u7885  h\u7859 n l\'e0 r\u7845 t nhanh s\u7869  g\u7863 p m\u7863 t th\'f4i.\
