\f1\b0 \cf2 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905 , ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng d\u7921 a v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7841 nh T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, trong l\'fac b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c ng\u7911  m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u b\u7883  lay t\u7881 nh, v\u7915 a m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra li\u7873 n nh\'ecn th\u7845 y g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t ph\'f3ng \u273 \u7841 i c\u7911 a b\u7841 n m\'ecnh. T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7867  m\u7863 t m\u7901  m\u7883 t ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , ch\'fang ta \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 th\u7871  n\'e0o? T\u7841 i sao l\u7841 i \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y? T\'f4i v\u7915 a m\u7899 i ra ngo\'e0i xem th\u7917  m\u7897 t v\'f2ng, trong th\'f4n kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ai c\u7843 . M\'e0 sao t\'f4i l\u7841 i b\u7845 t t\u7881 nh? H\'f4m qua c\u7853 u b\u7843 o t\'f4i \u273 i l\u7845 y h\'e0nh l\'fd, l\'fac l\'ean l\u7847 u m\u7903  c\u7917 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\'f4 b\'e9 con \'f4ng ch\u7911  c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i t\'f4i, sau \u273 \'f3 t\u7921  nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  n\'e0y m\u7897 t l\u7901 i kh\'f3 n\'f3i h\u7871 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u k\u7875  t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u cho h\u7855 n. V\'ec v\u7853 y v\u7895  v\u7895  h\u7855 n \'fd b\u7843 o tr\'e1nh qua m\u7897 t b\'ean, \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda t\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u432 \u7907 ng th\u7847 n kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c g\'ec h\'f4m qua c\u7853 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y l\'fac ban ng\'e0y, v\u7851 n th\u7845 p b\'e9 nh\u432  \u273 \u7891 ng t\u7917 , \u273 eo m\u7863 t n\u7841  m\'e0u v\'e0ng \u273 en, m\u7863 c \'e1o b\'e0o g\u7845 m, kh\'f4ng h\u7873  cao l\u7899 n nh\u432  \u273 \'eam qua c\u7853 u th\u7845 y. Cho n\'ean c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i \u273 \'eam qua, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c do \'e1nh n\u7871 n g\'e2y ra, hay l\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 c\u7889  t\'ecnh h\'f3a trang th\'e0nh th\u7847 n linh trong mi\u7871 u gi\u7843  th\u7847 n gi\u7843  qu\u7927 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n l\'e0 g\'ec, xem ra \'edt nh\u7845 t b\'e2y gi\u7901  b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 ang an to\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m: "Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u273 \u7915 ng h\u7887 i g\'ec c\u7843 , ch\'fang ta mau r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y \u273 \'e3, \u273 \u7907 i ra kh\u7887 i n\u417 i n\'e0y r\u7891 i t\'f4i s\u7869  k\u7875  l\u7841 i m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n cho c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ean ngo\'e0i mi\uc0\u7871 u m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i r\u7921 c r\u7905  tr\'ean cao, th\u7901 i ti\u7871 t d\u7877  ch\u7883 u, tr\u417 \u768 i cao xanh, gi\'f3 xu\'e2n \u7845 m \'e1p, trong th\'f4n l\u7841 i im \u7855 ng nh\u432  t\u7901 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\'fat sinh kh\'ed n\'e0o, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c nh\u7899  t\u7899 i chi ti\u7871 t l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u m\'ecnh c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng \u7893 n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n\'97\'97 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\'e0o th\'f4n l\'e0 bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i, trong \u273 \'eam th\u7853 t s\u7921  qu\'e1 y\'ean t\u297 nh. Qu\'ea \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u7903  g\u7847 n v\'f9ng n\'f4ng th\'f4n, n\u259 m b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i qua \u273 \u7901 i c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng c\'f9ng \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\'e0 m\u7865  tr\u7903  l\u7841 i qu\'ea \'f4ng m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 ng\u7911  l\u7841 i nh\'e0 h\u7885  h\'e0ng, c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng g\'e0 g\'e1y ch\'f3 s\u7911 a, c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng c\'f4n tr\'f9ng k\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 b\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  \u273 ang l\'e0 \u273 \u7847 u xu\'e2n, nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u259 ng, v\u7841 n v\u7853 t s\u7889 ng l\u7841 i, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng trong th\'f4n kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y b\u7845 t k\u7923  \'e2m thanh g\'ec c\u7911 a \u273 \u7897 ng v\u7853 t, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\u7845 t k\u7923  d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u c\u7911 a s\u7921  s\u7889 ng n\'e0o ngo\'e0i c\'e1c "Th\'f4n d\'e2n". Ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t gi\'e1c ra \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe m\'e1y c\uc0\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 h\u7871 t x\u259 ng, nh\u432 ng xe T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7851 n \u273 ang d\u7915 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a nh\'e0 tr\u7885 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i l\u7901 i n\'e0o, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng, nh\'ecn c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng hoang v\u7855 ng ti\'eau \u273 i\u7873 u trong th\'f4n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\'f3c g\'e1y d\u7921 ng \u273 \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7917 a nh\'e0 tr\u7885  m\u7903  r\u7897 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 i v\'e0o nh\'ecn k\u7929 , \'e1nh m\u7855 t l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 l\u432 \u7899 t v\'e0o trong c\u7917 a\'97\'97 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\'e3 tr\'ean qu\u7847 y \u7903  c\u7917 a, c\'e1nh tay n\u7893 i \u273 \u7847 y thi ban bu\'f4ng th\'f5ng tr\'ean m\u7863 t qu\u7847 y, d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'e1y ch\u417 i game ki\u7875 u c\u361  b\u7883  g\'e3y l\'e0m \u273 \'f4i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng chuy\u7875 n t\u7847 m m\u7855 t, c\u7853 u s\u7907  l\u7841 i sinh th\'eam chuy\u7879 n, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 i v\'e0o x\'e1c nh\u7853 n \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 thi th\u7875  ai, ch\u7881  gi\u7909 c T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m mau kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng xe ch\u7841 y ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi b\u7885 n h\u7885  ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7847 u con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7887  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, tr\u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 n n\u417 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n chi\u7871 c xe c\u417  gi\u7899 i ba b\'e1nh \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3, l\'fac n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i b\u7843 o T\u7889 ng C\u7843 m d\u7915 ng xe, k\u7875  l\u7841 i to\'e0n b\u7897  s\u7921  vi\u7879 c x\u7843 y ra trong th\'f4n, nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 tr\u7843 i qua trong l\'fac h\u7855 n h\'f4n m\'ea v\'e0 nh\u7919 ng ph\u7887 ng \u273 o\'e1n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i xem x\'e9t k\u7929  c\'e0ng c\u7843 nh v\u7853 t xung quanh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng c\uc0\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f2n m\u7897 t nghi v\u7845 n kh\'f4ng xua \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nghe Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\u7875  xong s\u7919 ng s\u7901  r\u7891 i h\u7891 i l\'e2u, l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "N\'e0y th\u7853 t l\'e0..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\u7901 i n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra. \u272 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y, m\u7885 i ng\'f4n t\u7915  \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7903  n\'ean kh\'f4 c\u7913 ng, kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1, c\u361 ng kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  mi\'eau t\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \u273 i theo Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7887  kia, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nghi ng\u7901  n\'f3i: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , c\u7853 u xem con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng th\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i r\u7845 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u432 ? V\'ec sao h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 ch\'fang ta c\'f9ng Ti\u7875 u L\'fd t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y \u273 i\u7873 u tra \u273 i t\u7899 i \u273 i lui hai v\'f2ng v\'e0o ban ng\'e0y v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec khi \u273 \'f3 to\'e0n b\u7897  th\'f4n, bao g\u7891 m c\u7843  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0o th\'f4n \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  qu\u7927  kh\'ed bao ph\u7911 , n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i th\u7901 i gian \u273 \u7863 c th\'f9, ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  tr\'fang Ch\u432 \u7899 ng Nh\'e3n Ph\'e1p." 
\f2\i (thu\uc0\u7853 t che m\u7855 t) 
\f1\i0 \uc0\u272 \'e2y c\u361 ng l\'e0 \u273 i\u7875 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi ho\u7863 c\'97\'97 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec nguy\'ean nh\'e2n g\'ec m\'e0 khi \u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y th\'f4n qu\'e1i \u273 \u7843 n kia?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn xung quanh h\u7891 i l\'e2u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ra manh m\u7889 i. \u7902  \u273 \'e2y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 s\'f3ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng g\u7917 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin nh\u7855 n, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i l\'e1i xe tr\u7903  l\u7841 i tr\u7845 n Ph\u432 \u7907 ng Th\u7911 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'e1o c\'e1o t\'ecnh h\'ecnh c\'f4ng t\'e1c, \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u li\u7873 n c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7897 i mang theo thi\u7871 t b\u7883  t\u7899 i, d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  ch\u7881  d\u7851 n c\u7911 a T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n chi\u7871 c xe c\u417  gi\u7899 i. Con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f3 r\u7845 t h\u7865 p, \'f4 t\'f4 kh\'f4ng \u273 i v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, b\u7885 n h\u7885  li\u7873 n thu\'ea hai chi\u7871 c xe x\'edch l\'f4 trong tr\u7845 n ch\u7903  thi\u7871 t b\u7883  c\u7847 n thi\u7871 t \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7893 i m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c xe m\'e1y kh\'e1c \u273 i theo. K\u7923  th\u7853 t l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  \u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \u7907 i, nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec nghi ho\u7863 c ch\u432 a r\'f5 kia, c\u7853 u nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 mu\u7889 n \u273 i c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn c\uc0\u7843 nh s\'e1t ch\u7909 p \u7843 nh l\u432 u gi\u7919  ch\u7913 ng c\u7913  xong k\'e9o chi\u7871 c xe ra kh\u7887 i m\u432 \u417 ng. C\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng g\u7847 n \u273 \'f3, \u273 \'fang l\'fac tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y v\u7883  tr\'ed b\u7883  chi\u7871 c xe ch\u7863 n l\u7841 i trong m\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\u7879 t chu sa ch\u432 a b\u7883  qu\u7865 t \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chu sa kia m\'e0u s\uc0\u7855 c c\u7921 c thu\u7847 n, h\u417 i t\u7889 i h\u417 n m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i, t\u432 \u417 ng ph\u7843 n v\u7899 i m\'e0u v\'e0ng n\'e2u c\u7911 a \u273 \u7845 t trong m\u432 \u417 ng, m\u7863 c d\'f9 kh\'f4ng s\'e1ng nh\u432 ng g\u7847 n nh\u432  ngay t\u7913 c kh\u7855 c l\'e0m c\u7853 u ch\'f3i m\u7855 t. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 \u273 i t\u7899 i, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng mu\u7889 n nh\'ecn r\'f5 h\u417 n. V\u7879 t chu sa kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng th\u7859 ng t\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 c\'f3 th\'eam m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ch\'e9o ngang, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n c\u7911 a h\'ecnh tam gi\'e1c\'97\'97 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tin t\u432 \u7903 ng m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n sai, m\'e0u s\u7855 c chu sa, h\'ecnh d\'e1ng k\'fd hi\u7879 u n\'e0y \'97\'97 \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 ph\u432 \u417 ng th\u7913 c v\u7869  tr\u7853 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u7903  Tr\'ec gia ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng ch\'ednh th\u7913 c h\u7885 c thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i ng\'e0y ng\'e0y nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\'e0u s\u7855 c chu sa n\'e0y, ng\'e0y ng\'e0y ng\u7855 m ngh\'eda h\'ecnh d\u7841 ng ph\'f9 tri\u7879 n tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p n\'e0y. V\u7873  sau c\u7853 u r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia, nh\u7919 ng cu\u7889 n s\'e1ch mang \u273 i c\u361 ng c\'f3 gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u c\'e1ch v\u7869  tr\u7853 n c\u417  b\u7843 n v\'e0 v\'e0i lo\u7841 i tr\u7853 n h\'ecnh tr\u7909  c\u7897 t nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t \'fd ngh\u297  x\u7865 t qua trong \u273 \u7847 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tim b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7853 p th\'ecnh th\u7883 ch. C\u7853 u lui hai b\u432 \u7899 c, m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh xung quanh. M\u7897 t nh\'e1nh c\'e2y b\u7883  nghi\'eang, ven \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 l\u7899 n, v\u7883  tr\'ed nguy\'ean b\u7843 n c\u7911 a chi\u7871 c xe b\u7883  l\u7853 t... \u273 \u7873 u d\u7847 n h\u7907 p th\'e0nh m\u7897 t v\'f2ng tr\'f2n, t\u7841 o th\'e0nh h\'ecnh d\u7841 ng m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n \u273 \u7891 . C\u7853 u v\u7851 n ch\u432 a nh\'ecn ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chi ti\u7871 t c\u7911 a tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p n\'e0y, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t ra t\u7915  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e9t t\u7893 ng th\u7875 , \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7909  \'e2m tr\u7853 n, m\u7895 i khi t\u7889 i \u273 \u7871 n sau khi m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i l\u7863 n n\'f3 s\u7869  d\u7847 n d\u7847 n d\u7851 n qu\u7927  kh\'ed b\'ean trong th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia h\u432 \u7899 ng ra \u273 \'e2y, do \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 m\u7903  ra m\u7897 t l\u7895  h\u7893 ng \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i qua \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y v\'e0 th\'f4n kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m nh\'e0 Chu Huy m\u7845 t t\'edch, xe b\u7883  l\u7853 t v\'e0o trong m\u432 \u417 ng, tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p n\'e0y c\'f2n thi\u7871 u h\u7909 t, l\'e0 m\u7897 t h\'ecnh tr\'f2n ch\u432 a ho\'e0n ch\u7881 nh, cho n\'ean c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 c\u7889  t\'ecnh v\u7869  tr\u7853 n d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t trong m\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7875  bi\u7871 n tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p tr\u7903  n\'ean ho\'e0n ch\u7881 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 chi\uc0\u7871 c xe kia sau \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7897 ng tay \u273 \u7897 ng ch\'e2n, c\u7889  t\'ecnh b\'e0y \u7903  v\u7883  tr\'ed kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean n\'f3i gia \uc0\u273 \'ecnh nh\'e0 Chu Huy m\u7845 t t\'edch kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u7851 u nhi\'ean. D\'f9 l\'fac \u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p n\u7841 n th\'ec c\u361 ng s\u7869  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c g\u7863 p n\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i ch\uc0\u7871 t c\u7911 a hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t kia, \u273 \'e3 \u7903  trong d\u7921  li\u7879 u c\u7911 a m\u7897 t s\u7889  ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i thao t\'fang l\'ean k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch. Qu\u7927  th\'f4n kia ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c l\'e0 do nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 c\u7889  t\'ecnh d\u7851 n \u273 \u7871 n, nh\u432 ng sau khi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n d\u7883  bi\u7871 n \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia \u273 \'e3 c\u7889  t\'ecnh l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng n\'f3 \u273 \u7875  h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  mu\u7889 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  \u259 n qu\u7927 , qu\u7927  \u259 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u259 n ng\u432 \u7901 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u7867  h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 qu\u7927 , hay ch\'ednh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 th\'e2n ph\u7853 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7899 c s\u7921  h\'ecnh th\'e0nh c\u7911 a qu\u7927  th\'f4n?\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  th\u7853 t s\u7921  mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i... l\'e0 ai?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\'f9ng s\u432  ph\u7909  ch\u7883 u tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m ch\u7881  d\u7851 n h\u7855 n trong \u273 \u7897 i c\u7843 nh s\'e1t \u273 ang \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 "... C\uc0\u7845 p tr\'ean \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t ch\u7881  \u273 \'edch danh c\u7853 u ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch v\u7909  m\u7845 t t\'edch n\'e0y, t\'f4i c\'f2n \u273 ang lo m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i c\u7853 u l\u7841 i \u273 \'e0o ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nhi\u7873 u nh\u432  th\u7871 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m x\u7845 u h\u7893  c\u432 \u7901 i g\u432 \u7907 ng: "Kh\'f4ng, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u7841 , l\u7847 n n\'e0y ch\u7911  y\u7871 u l\'e0 nh\u7901  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n c\u7911 a con, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u7869  con c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\'e1i m\u7841 ng n\'e0y. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 s\u432  ph\u7909 , l\u7841 i n\'f3i ti\u7871 p chuy\u7879 n l\u7847 n n\'e0y th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m qu\u7927  d\u7883 ..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u b\'e0n b\u7841 c t\'ecnh ti\u7871 t v\u7909  \'e1n, l\'fac \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  Tr\'ec Di\'ean, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u hai ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "S\u432  ph\u7909 , \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7841 n con, b\u7885 n con quen nhau t\u7915  h\u7891 i c\u7845 p ba, quan h\u7879  c\u7921 c k\u7923  b\u7873 n ch\u7863 t, chuy\u7879 n l\u7847 n n\'e0y t\u7845 t c\u7843  l\'e0 nh\u7901  c\'f3 c\u7853 u \u7845 y \u7841 ."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7841 i gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u432  ph\u7909  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\'e0o h\uc0\u7887 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, m\u7845 y c\'e2u sau t\u7887  v\u7867  thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng h\u7887 i: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng r\u7845 t n\u7893 i danh h\u7843  ch\'fa? V\u7915 a r\u7891 i ch\'e1u nghe th\u7845 y ch\'fa n\'f3i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t giao b\u7843 n \'e1n n\'e0y cho T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u432  ph\u7909  h\u7855 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f4ng m\u7845 y b\u7853 n t\'e2m \u273 \'e1p: "\u272 \'fang v\u7853 y, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  Ti\u7875 u T\u7889 ng r\'e8n luy\u7879 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i c\'e1c c\u7853 u l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra chuy\u7879 n th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia k\u7923  qu\'e1i nh\u432  th\u7871 . Th\'f4n n\'e0y v\u7889 n h\u7867 o l\'e1nh, t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u m\'f9a \u273 \'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n nay l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai v\'e0o th\'f4n, ng\u432 \u7901 i trong th\'f4n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec m\'e0 \u273 i ra, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ai coi l\'e0 c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , kh\'f4ng ai ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c trong th\'f4n t\u7915 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ai n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a r\u7891 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\'e0o trong th\'f4n xem x\'e9t, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra thi th\u7875  c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'e2n, theo ph\'e1n \u273 o\'e1n s\u417  b\u7897  th\u7901 i gian t\u7917  vong v\'e0 nguy\'ean nh\'e2n t\u7917  vong c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nhau. Th\u7901 i gian t\u7917  vong t\u7915  ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\'e1ch nhau ch\u7915 ng h\u417 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 thi th\u7875  n\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7849 m li\u7879 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho d\'f9 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\uc0\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927  t\'e1c lo\u7841 n, nh\u7919 ng \u7843 o gi\'e1c h\u432  h\u432  th\u7921 c th\u7921 c m\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \'e3 tr\u7843 i qua r\u7891 i b\'e1o c\'e1o l\u7841 i th\'ec chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7911  qu\u7927  d\u7883  \'97\'97 gia \u273 \'ecnh m\u7897 t nh\'e0, v\u7907  ch\u7871 t nh\u432 ng ch\u7891 ng c\'f2n s\u7889 ng, v\'ec sao l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7841  t\'e1ng ch\'f4n c\u7845 t cho v\u7907 ? C\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o th\u7901 i gian t\u7917  vong, trong gia \u273 \'ecnh c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t, c\'f2n l\u7841 i hai, ba ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng. M\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i trong th\'f4n \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y x\'e1c ch\u7871 t, t\u7841 i sao m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f2n s\u7889 ng kia kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng g\'ec m\'e0 v\u7851 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c s\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng cho \u273 \u7871 n khi ch\'ednh m\'ecnh c\u361 ng ch\u7871 t \u273 i? Khi t\u7845 t c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i trong th\'f4n \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i, ng\u432 \u7901 i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\'f2n s\u7889 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 suy ngh\u297  g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng \'fd ngh\u297  n\'e0y l\'e0m \'f4ng kh\'f4ng r\'e9t m\'e0 run, ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7847 u c\u361 ng \u273 au, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian t\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7869  ph\u7843 i kh\u7893  n\'e3o v\'ec v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia n\'e0y, cho n\'ean hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd \u273 \u7871 n c\'e2u h\u7887 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean. \'d4ng c\'f4ng t\'e1c nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m, kinh nghi\u7879 m phong ph\'fa, m\u7863 c d\'f9 bi\u7871 t T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\'fac \u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7853 n ch\u7913 c l\'e0 v\'ec nh\u7901  ch\'fat quan h\u7879 , nh\u432 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 ch\'ed ti\u7871 n th\u7911 , l\'e0m vi\u7879 c c\u361 ng n\u7895  l\u7921 c c\'f3 tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m, \'f4ng c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7903 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 c\'f3 th\'e0nh ki\u7871 n v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c n\'ean ch\u7881  b\u7843 o n\'ean truy\u7873 n th\u7909 , c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\'fap \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\'e8n luy\u7879 n \'f4ng \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0m. L\u7847 n n\'e0y c\u7845 p tr\'ean ch\u7881  \u273 \'edch danh T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 i ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch \'e1n m\u7845 t t\'edch n\'e0y, \'f4ng ch\u7881  cho l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i quen nh\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u7889  \'fd mu\u7889 n cho h\u7855 n c\u417  h\u7897 i r\'e8n luy\u7879 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 \u273 \u7875  \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u tr\u7843  l\u7901 i li\u7873 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\u7897 i t\'e2m ch\u7907 t l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7921 a v\'e0o s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh v\'e0 quy\u7873 n l\u7921 c c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia, mu\u7889 n l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 qu\u7843  th\u7921 c d\u7877  nh\u432  tr\u7903  b\'e0n tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean ph\uc0\u7843 i n\'f3i l\'e0... k\u7923  th\u7853 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng qu\u7927  th\'f4n n\'e0y, ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c b\u7885 n h\u7885  mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\'ecnh? D\'f9 l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\'f4ng nh\u7901  m\'ecnh gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng r\u7891 i c\'f9ng nhau \u273 \u7871 n th\'f4n n\'e0y th\'ec b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng quan h\u7879  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m m\'e0 d\u7851 n m\'ecnh t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u. M\'ecnh v\'e0 Tr\'ec gia nh\u432  con ki\u7871 n v\'e0 c\'e2y \u273 \u7841 i th\u7909 , hu\u7889 ng chi m\'ecnh ngo\'e0i s\'e1ng Tr\'ec gia trong t\u7889 i, n\u7871 u Tr\'ec Dung ho\u7863 c Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  n\u7893 i s\'e1t t\'e2m v\u7899 i m\'ecnh th\'ec vi\u7879 c h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t m\'ecnh qu\u7843  th\u7921 c v\'f4 c\'f9ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng, \u273 \'e2u c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i hao ph\'ed c\'f4ng phu l\u7899 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\u432 \u7907 n quanh m\u7897 t v\'f2ng lu\u7849 n qu\u7849 n l\u7899 n th\u7871  n\'e0y, c\'f2n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t oan bao nhi\'eau m\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'f4 t\u7897 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7915  phi... b\u7885 n h\u7885  e ng\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\u432 u l\u7841 i ch\u7913 ng c\u7913  m\u432 u h\u7841 i c\u7853 u, cho n\'ean m\u7899 i c\u7889  \'fd ch\u7885 n c\'e1ch th\u7913 c phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u7881  \u273 \u7875  khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u th\u7847 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t qu\u7927  kh\'f4ng hay m\'e0 ch\u7871 t trong qu\u7927  th\'f4n n\'e0y, l\'e0m cho t\u7845 t c\u7843  tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  chuy\u7879 n ngo\'e0i \'fd mu\u7889 n. Ch\u7881  c\u7847 n sau \u273 \'f3 h\u7911 y giao l\u7897  t\u7909  \'e2m tr\u7853 n kia \u273 i, n\u7871 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \u273 i\u7873 u tra, c\u259 n b\u7843 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tra ra manh m\u7889 i g\'ec.\cb1 \
