\f1\b0 \cf2 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n t\'e1ch kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia. C\u7853 u h\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7847 u thai l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, \u273 o\u7841 n tuy\u7879 t kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ch\'fat quan h\u7879  g\'ec v\u7899 i Tr\'ec gia, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n b\u7845 t c\u7913  th\u7913  g\'ec c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia. Nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao c\u7853 u v\u7851 n mang danh ph\u7853 n ch\'e1u \u273 \'edch t\'f4n, ch\u7881  ri\'eang \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y, ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, ngay c\u7843  Tr\'ec Dung c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng y\'ean b\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u7853 u ngh\u297  r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e1i gai trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Dung, r\'fat ra v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \u273 \u7911 , ph\u7843 i ph\'e1 hu\u7927  ho\'e0n to\'e0n Tr\'ec Dung m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  y\'ean t\'e2m s\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1t \'fd c\uc0\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 r\'f5 nh\u432  th\u7871 , c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  khoanh tay ch\u7883 u ch\u7871 t, n\u7871 u \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh gi\u7871 t c\u7853 u, c\'f3 l\u7847 n m\u7897 t \u7855 t s\u7869  c\'f3 l\u7847 n hai. Nh\u7901  c\'f3 v\u7883  "Th\u7847 n linh" kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t t\'ean kia c\u7853 u m\u7899 i tho\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ki\u7871 p, l\u7847 n sau ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c s\u7869  c\'f3 v\u7853 n kh\'ed t\u7889 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7871  \u273 \u417 n l\u7921 c b\u7841 c, mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\'f3 Thi\'ean s\u432  th\u7871  gia th\u7847 n b\'ed kh\'f3 l\u432 \u7901 ng v\u7851 n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n qu\'e1 kh\'f3 kh\u259 n, kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c g\'ec chuy\u7879 n hoang \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tr\uc0\u7903  l\u7841 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\u297  r\u7845 t l\'e2u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p n\'e0o \u7893 n th\u7887 a c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng. K\u7871 t qu\u7843  duy nh\u7845 t ngh\u297  ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\'ednh l\'e0 \'edt nh\u7845 t c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i tr\u7903  l\u7841 i trong gi\u7899 i, \u273 \u7875  c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432  v\'e0 nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i nghi\'ean c\u7913 u thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, nh\u432  v\u7853 y Tr\'ec gia s\u7869  e ng\u7841 i thanh danh c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i suy t\'ednh th\'eam, m\'e0 c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  tranh th\u7911  th\u7901 i gian gi\'e0nh th\'eam th\u7867  b\'e0i b\u7843 o to\'e0n t\'ednh m\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng do d\u7921  n\u7919 a, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7863 t v\'e9 \u273 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  L, c\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, s\u7855 p x\u7871 p \u7893 n th\u7887 a chuy\u7879 n trong nh\'e0 xong l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng. C\u7853 u s\u7855 p t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i lu\u7853 n v\u259 n \u273 \'e3 vi\u7871 t xong, ch\u7881  c\'f2n thi\u7871 u ph\u7847 n k\u7871 t lu\u7853 n n\'ean vi\u7879 c tr\'ean tr\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u, l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n c\'f9ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7899 i l\u7847 n n\'e0y \u273 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  L \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i trong d\'f2ng t\u7897 c Thi\'ean s\u432  th\u7871  gia gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  Tr\'ec gia c\u7921 c k\'ec kh\'f3 t\'ecm, c\u361 ng kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7855 t g\u7863 p, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng d\'f9 g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 thi\'ean s\u432  giao ti\u7871 p v\u7899 i qu\u7927  th\u7847 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia d\'f9 mu\u7889 n t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y m\u7903  qu\'e1n c\'e0 ph\'ea \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  L.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a gia gi\u7889 ng Tr\'ec gia, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 Thi\'ean s\u432  th\u7871  gia r\u7845 t truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\u7899 n h\u417 n c\u7853 u n\u7917 a tu\u7893 i, c\u7853 u v\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y xem nh\u432  quen bi\u7871 t t\u7915  nh\u7887 , nh\u432 ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'ednh c\'e1ch kh\'f4ng h\u7907 p, quan h\u7879  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng. Cha H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\'e0 con th\u7913  c\u7911 a H\u7913 a gia, b\u7903 i v\'ec r\u7845 t c\'f3 thi\'ean ph\'fa v\u7899 i thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p n\'ean \u7903  H\u7913 a gia \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883  kh\'e1 cao. H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t em g\'e1i sinh \u273 \'f4i, ng\u432 \u7901 i x\u432 a v\u7851 n th\u432 \u7901 ng n\'f3i sinh \u273 \'f4i l\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 m x\u7845 u, nh\u432 ng v\'ec cha m\u7865  H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng hai con c\u7911 a m\'ecnh n\'ean hai anh em H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y khi c\'f2n nh\u7887  \u7903  H\u7913 a gia \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ti\u7875 u c\'f4ng ch\'faa ti\u7875 u thi\u7871 u gia kh\'f4ng ai d\'e1m tr\'eau ch\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'e1ch quan m\'e0 n\'f3i thu\u7903  nh\u7887  m\'ecnh v\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y kh\'f4ng h\u7907 p m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n nguy\'ean nh\'e2n c\'f3 th\u7875  v\'ec m\'ecnh ghen t\u7925  v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, ghen t\u7925  h\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7853 c cha ch\'fa tr\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7889 i b\u7843 o v\u7879  che ch\u7903 . H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y th\'ec kh\'f4ng quen nh\'ecn c\u7853 u m\u7873 m m\u7873 m nh\u361 n nh\u361 n qu\u7845 n b\'ean c\u7841 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, n\'f3i c\u7853 u c\'f2n kh\'f4ng m\u7841 nh m\u7869  b\u7857 ng con g\'e1i, kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng nam t\u7917  h\'e1n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 H\u7913 a H\'e2n em g\'e1i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd, H\u7913 a H\'e2n gh\'e9t b\u7887  anh trai th\'e0nh ki\u7871 n v\u7899 i gi\u7899 i t\'ednh c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, ai n\'f3i c\u7913  l\'e0 con g\'e1i th\'ec s\u7869  m\u7873 m m\u7873 m nh\u361 n nh\u361 n; Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'ec kh\'f4ng th\'edch H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y xen v\'e0o vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, chuy\u7879 n c\u7853 u th\'edch qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  r\u7891 i qu\u7845 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n xen v\'e0o. Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\'ednh t\'ecnh ch\u7853 m, l\'e0m vi\u7879 c c\u361 ng nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng ki\'ean nh\u7851 n, cho n\'ean quan h\u7879  v\u7899 i H\u7913 a H\'e2n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho \uc0\u273 \u7871 n n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m tu\u7893 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 anh em H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y H\u7913 a H\'e2n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n c\'f9ng nhau t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng s\u7889 ng t\u7915  trong ch\u7895  ch\u7871 t, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7899 i c\'f3 ch\'fat c\u7843 m gi\'e1c *tinh tinh t\u432 \u417 ng t\'edch, r\u7891 i b\u7903 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 c\'f3 th\'eam m\u7897 t m\u7889 i giao t\'ecnh \u273 \'e1ng qu\'fd c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7907  gi\'fap nhau.\cb1 \
