\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi r\uc0\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia t\u7921  nhi\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i hai anh em H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi l\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c c\'f3 m\u7897 t l\u7847 n c\'f9ng b\u7841 n h\u7885 c \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  L ch\u417 i, trong l\'fac v\'f4 t\'ecnh ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t ti\u7879 m c\'e0 ph\'ea r\u7845 t n\u7893 i ti\u7871 ng \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  L l\'e0 do H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y r\u7843 nh r\u7895 i m\u7903 , \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y kh\'f4ng thi\u7871 u ti\u7873 n, m\u7903  ti\u7879 m ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\'ec s\u7903  th\'edch. C\u361 ng may m\u7855 n nh\u7901  c\'f3 cha m\u7865  dung t\'fang, h\u7855 n v\'e0 H\u7913 a H\'e2n m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  "T\u7921  do ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n" nh\u432  v\u7853 y. H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i h\u7855 n gh\'e9t b\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng m\'e0 h\u7911  l\u7853 u c\u7911 a H\u7913 a gia n\'ean m\u7899 i ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y, th\'e0 t\u7921  m\'ecnh m\u7903  ti\u7879 m ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n quay v\u7873 , c\u361 ng n\'f3i sau n\'e0y n\u7871 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec th\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7879 m t\'ecm h\u7855 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean hi\u7875 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'f3 c\u7911 a H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, nh\u432 ng quan h\u7879  c\u7911 a hai anh em v\u7899 i cha h\u7885  kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng m\'ecnh, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7855 t \u273 \u7913 t v\u7899 i H\u7913 a gia m\'e0 g\u7855 n ch\u7863 t v\u7899 i gia t\u7897 c v\'e0 gi\u7899 i thi\'ean s\u432 . N\u7871 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean mu\u7889 n tr\u7903  l\u7841 i trong gi\u7899 i, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i trung gian duy nh\u7845 t c\'f3 th\u7875  th\'f4ng qua ch\u7881  c\'f3 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7879 m c\'e0 ph\'ea \u273 \'fang l\'fac H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 ang \u7903  \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ch\uc0\u7911  H\u7913 a \u273 \'edch th\'e2n chi\'eau \u273 \'e3i c\u7853 u: "Mu\u7889 n u\u7889 ng g\'ec, t\'f4i l\'e0m cho c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn menu: "S\uc0\u7919 a chocolate, th\'eam \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y "Ch\u7853 c" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i pha s\u7919 a cho c\u7853 u, ti\u7879 n th\u7875  c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7841 o n\'f3i: "Ng\'e0i \u273 \'fang l\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\u7913 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7919 a nh\u7881 , Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u gia."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y r\'f3t cho m\'ecnh m\u7897 t c\u7889 c h\u7891 ng tr\'e0, mang s\u7919 a cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng ra sau ti\u7879 m ng\u7891 i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng l\'ean \u273 i\u7879 n tam b\u7843 o, l\u7847 n n\'e0y Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u gia \u273 \u7841 i gi\'e1 quang l\'e2m l\'e0 v\'ec chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t h\'f2a v\'e0 n\u7897 i t\'ecnh gi\u7919 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 Tr\'ec gia H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5, n\u7871 u \u273 \'e3 mu\u7889 n nh\u7901  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng gi\'fap, Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng g\u7841 t h\u7855 n, k\u7875  l\u7841 i ng\u7885 n ngu\u7891 n chuy\u7879 n \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia cho h\u7855 n nghe.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Cho n\'ean c\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Dung mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i c\u7853 u? Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n tr\u7903  l\u7841 i d\u432 \u7899 i t\u7847 m m\u7855 t c\u7911 a t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432 , quay v\u7873  gi\u7899 i, d\'f9ng c\'e1ch n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec Dung kh\'f4ng d\'e1m manh \u273 \u7897 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ph\uc0\u7843 i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean xoay c\u7889 c trong tay, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng n\u7871 u l\'e0m th\u7871 , Tr\'ec Dung th\u7845 y c\u7853 u c\'f3 d\u7921  \u273 \u7883 nh tr\u7903  v\u7873 , mu\u7889 n \u273 o\u7841 t l\u7841 i m\u7885 i th\u7913  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n. C\u7853 u ch\u7855 c s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7913 c Tr\'ec Dung gi\u7871 t c\u7853 u nhanh h\u417 n ch\u7913 ?" H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y cau m\'e0y n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\uc0\u7903  v\u7873  ch\u7871 t, kh\'f4ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u361 ng ch\u7871 t; \u273 o\u7841 t c\u361 ng ch\u7871 t, kh\'f4ng \u273 o\u7841 t c\u361 ng ch\u7871 t. Kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  li\u7873 u v\u7899 i h\u7855 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  n\'f3i, "T\'f4i c\'f3 quay v\u7873  hay kh\'f4ng, c\'f3 mu\u7889 n \u273 o\u7841 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n hay kh\'f4ng, h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  gi\u7871 t t\'f4i. D\'f9 sao t\'f4i c\u361 ng mang danh ch\'e1u \u273 \'edch t\'f4n, h\u417 n n\u7919 a v\u7851 n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec gia, t\'f4i tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432  \u273 \u7891 ng \u273 \u7841 o v\'e0 l\'e3o nh\'e2n trong t\u7897 c \u273 \u7873 u nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1m Tr\'ec Dung c\'f3 ra tay th\'ec \'edt nhi\u7873 u c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i ki\'eang n\u7875  m\u7845 y ph\u7847 n. Chung quy t\u7889 t h\u417 n so v\u7899 i l\'e0m m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean m\u7897 t ng\'e0y n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 ch\u7871 t kh\'f4ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng c\'f2n li\'ean l\u7909 y \u273 \u7871 n b\u7841 n b\'e8."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 i\u7873 u n\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \'fang." H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y tr\u7847 m t\u432  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, "V\u7915 a \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\u7917 a th\'e1ng n\u7919 a s\u7869  \u273 \u7871 n L\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i n\u259 m n\u259 m t\u7893  ch\u7913 c m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, l\u7847 n n\'e0y do ch\'ednh H\u7913 a gia ch\u7911  tr\'ec, hai ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c cha t\'f4i c\'f2n g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n gi\u7909 c t\'f4i v\u7873 , t\'f4i s\u7869  ngh\u297  c\'e1ch s\u7855 p x\u7871 p cho c\u7853 u th\'e2n ph\u7853 n v\u7915 a h\u7907 p l\'fd l\u7841 i v\u7915 a khi\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ch\'fa \'fd \u273 \u7875  d\u7851 n c\u7853 u tham gia."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7843 m \u417 n c\u7853 u." Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'f4ng linh gi\u7899 i thi\'ean s\u432  n\'e0y t\u7921  nh\u7853 n l\'e0 \u273 \'f3n th\u7847 n ti\u7877 n qu\u7927  ngh\u7883 ch thi\'ean c\u7843 i m\u7879 nh, \u273 \u7841 o tr\u7901 i c\'f3 ph\'fac, cho n\'ean th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7913  c\'e1ch m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian s\u7869  ti\u7871 n h\'e0nh nghi th\u7913 c t\u7871  tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7875  t\u7841  t\u7897 i c\u7847 u ph\'fac, d\u7847 n d\'e0 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh g\u7847 n nh\u432  t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432  c\'f9ng tham gia nghi th\u7913 c tr\u7885 ng \u273 \u7841 i n\'e0y, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7885 i l\'e0 "L\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i". Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i L\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7893  ch\u7913 c n\u259 m n\u259 m m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 thi\'ean s\u432  t\u7915  m\u7897 t ph\'e1i c\'f3 uy v\u7885 ng \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7911  tr\'ec, l\u7847 n n\'e0y v\u7915 a v\u7863 n \u273 \u7871 n phi\'ean H\u7913 a gia. H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng quay v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u7843  bu\u7893 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, ch\u7881  ch\u7853 m r\'e3i u\u7889 ng tr\'e0, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang t\u7921  h\u7887 i n\'ean d\'f9ng c\'e1ch g\'ec \u273 \u7875  mang Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay v\u7873  tham gia l\u7877 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889 c s\u7913  tr\u7855 ng \u273 \u7921 ng n\u432 \u7899 c tr\'e0 d\u7847 n th\u7845 y \u273 \'e1y, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y b\u7843 o Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\u7889 c, \u273 i ra l\u7845 y th\'eam tr\'e0, n\u259 m ph\'fat sau b\u432 ng m\u7897 t c\u7889 c h\u7891 ng tr\'e0 v\'e0o, gi\u7919 a l\'f4ng m\'e0y l\u7897  ra v\'e0i ph\u7847 n gi\u7843 o ho\u7841 t: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, t\'f4i c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\'e1ch \u7893 n th\u7887 a r\u7891 i, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n c\u7853 u c\'f3 \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd hay kh\'f4ng th\'f4i. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i t\'f4i v\u7899 i Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n v\u7851 n \u273 ang \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n, c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7885 n gi\u7843  l\'e0m b\u7841 n trai t\'f4i ho\u7863 c b\u7841 n trai Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n, l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i l\u7847 n n\'e0y theo v\u7873 . Nh\u432  v\u7853 y s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n t\'ecm c\u7899  kh\'e1c, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i g\'ec, ch\'fang ta quen bi\u7871 t t\u7915  nh\u7887 , \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean y\'eau nhau m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nghi ng\u7901 ."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y qu\u7843  th\u7853 t c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e1ch, anh em H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \u7873 u b\u7857 ng l\'f2ng hi sinh b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7875  gi\'fap c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u273 \u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ch\u7885 n gi\u7843  l\'e0m b\u7841 n trai Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n, gi\u7843  l\'e0m b\u7841 n trai c\u7853 u th\'ec ch\u432 a c\u7847 n ch\u7901  Tr\'ec Dung ra tay b\'e1c trai \u273 \'e3 di\u7879 t t\'f4i tr\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i, "Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n ch\u432 a? C\'f4 \u7845 y c\'f3 \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd kh\'f4ng?" L\'e3o nh\'e2n \u273 \u7841 i gia t\u7897 c H\u7913 a gia r\u7845 t c\u7893  h\u7911 , n\u7871 u H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y t\'ecm "B\u7841 n trai" nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  b\u7883  ph\u7843 n \u273 \u7889 i k\u7883 ch li\u7879 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n sinh th\'eam r\u7855 c r\u7889 i. \u272 \'e1nh gi\'e1 kh\'e1ch quan th\'ec H\u7913 a H\'e2n l\'e0 con g\'e1i \'fat, \u7903  trong gia t\u7897 c t\u432  t\u432 \u7903 ng tr\u7885 ng nam khinh n\u7919  nghi\'eam tr\u7885 ng n\'e0y v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c coi tr\u7885 ng m\u7845 y, \u273 i\u7875 m t\u7889 t l\'e0 kh\'f4ng b\u7883  qu\u7843 n th\'fac qu\'e1 m\u7913 c. N\u7871 u d\'f9ng th\'e2n ph\u7853 n b\u7841 n trai H\u7913 a H\'e2n \u273 \u7875  tr\u7903  v\u7873 , v\u7853 y c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch khi\u7871 n Tr\'ec Dung s\u7907  n\'e9m chu\u7897 t v\u7905  b\'ecnh m\'e0 c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\'ednh to\'e1n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng g\'e2y ra qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u ch\'fa \'fd v\'e0 phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u361 ng c\u432 \u7901 i: "C\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t t\'ednh con b\'e9 r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y, chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i n\'f3 kh\'f4ng v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , l\u7841 i l\'e0 v\'ec gi\'fap c\u7853 u, ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd. N\'f3 b\u7843 o t\u7889 i nay s\u7869  t\u7899 i t\'ecm t\'f4i r\u7891 i c\'f9ng v\u7873  nh\'e0, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec c\u7853 u c\u7913  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n th\u7859 ng n\'f3 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1u gi\uc0\u7901  t\u7889 i H\u7913 a H\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n, nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p v\u7867  ngo\'e0i c\'f4 n\'e0ng h\u417 i kh\'e1c \u273 i ch\'fat, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra b\u7897  d\u7841 ng ti\u7875 u c\'f4 n\u432 \u417 ng n\u259 m n\'e0o, t\'ednh c\'e1ch ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng thay \u273 \u7893 i, nghe Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i xong li\u7873 n kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921  \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng. Sau \u273 \'f3 hai anh em gi\u7919  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  L ch\u417 i hai ng\'e0y, \u273 \u7907 i ba ng\'e0y sau c\'f9ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  quay v\u7873  H\u7913 a gia tham gia L\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c khi \u273 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 o\'e1n chuy\u7871 n n\'e0y m\'ecnh ph\u7843 i \u273 i m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian n\'ean \u273 \'e3 thu\'ea ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'fap vi\u7879 c cho \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng \u273 \u7871 n l\'e0m b\u7919 a tr\u432 a v\'e0 b\u7919 a t\u7889 i, d\u7885 n d\u7865 p nh\'e0 c\u7917 a. C\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u259 m s\'f3c ngo\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  y\'ean t\'e2m h\u417 n, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \'fang gi\u7901  g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n v\u7873  nh\'e0 l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7845 y ng\'e0y nay Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 H\u7913 a H\'e2n \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  nh\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y. Bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\'e0y \u273 i, H\u7913 a H\'e2n v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  tr\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7901 i ti\u7871 t r\u7845 t \u273 \u7865 p, tr\u259 ng s\'e1ng sao th\u432 a, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean mua \'edt \u273 \u7891  n\u432 \u7899 ng v\'e0 bia v\u7873 , m\u7863 c \'e1o kho\'e1c ng\u7891 i tr\'ean s\'e2n th\u432 \u7907 ng h\'f3ng gi\'f3, v\u7915 a u\u7889 ng v\u7915 a xem b\'f3ng \u273 \'e1.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7891 i ngo\'e0i tr\u7901 i l\'e2u d\u7847 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\u7841 nh, bia c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 u\u7889 ng kh\'e1 nhi\u7873 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a \u273 \u7883 nh b\u7843 o H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y v\'e0o trong nh\'e0, ch\u7907 t nghe H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c, hai ng\'e0y qua t\'f4i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe ng\uc0\u7919  kh\'ed c\u7911 a h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7855 m, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i v\'ec u\u7889 ng nhi\u7873 u hay v\'ec qu\u7843  th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng t\u7847 m th\u432 \u7901 ng hay kh\'f4ng, quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n: "Chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\'e1m l\u7845 y kh\'f4ng?" H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng v\'e0o m\u7855 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t y\u7871 t h\u7847 u, h\u7841  m\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, t\u7887  v\u7867  t\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 nh\u7899 . C\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean g\u7863 p t\'f4i trong ti\u7879 m, ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u b\'f3ng gi\'f3 h\u7887 i t\'f4i v\u7873  ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , t\'f4i c\u7889  t\'ecnh gi\u7843  v\u7901  nghe kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u nh\u432 ng th\u7853 t ra l\'e0 t\'f4i s\u7907  t\'f4i l\u7855 m mi\u7879 ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean n\'f3i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng l\u7847 n n\'e0y tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  g\u7863 p ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3, cho n\'ean t\'f4i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  c\u7853 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y nh\'ecn nh\u432  \u273 ang c\'e2n nh\u7855 c t\u7915  ng\u7919 : "M\u7845 y n\u259 m nay t\'f4i l\u7845 y c\u7899  \u273 i h\u7885 c m\u7903  ti\u7879 m n\'e0y, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  xa H\u7913 a gia, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c truy\u7873 n mi\u7879 ng \u273 \u7871 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c to\'e0n di\u7879 n v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 . T\'f4i ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t ba n\u259 m sau khi c\u7853 u \u273 i, hai anh trai c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t qua \u273 \u7901 i, h\u7855 n tr\u7903  th\'e0nh ch\u7911  nh\'e2n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p gia. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ph\'e0m l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n, m\u7895 i khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y h\u7855 n nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i h\u7855 n \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  v\'f4 c\'f9ng th\u7853 n tr\u7885 ng k\'ednh c\u7849 n, ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n cha t\'f4i, ngay c\u7843  \'f4ng t\'f4i \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n c\u361 ng r\u7845 t khi\'eam nh\u432 \u7901 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\u7849 n th\u7853 n nh\'ecn n\'e9t m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n n\'f3i: "Cho n\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'e0, th\u7901 i gian c\'f3 th\u7875  thay \u273 \u7893 i m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, hu\u7889 ng chi \u273 \'e3 nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 thay \u273 \u7893 i nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u l\'e0 g\'ec. C\'f3 l\u7869  h\u7855 n... \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e0 c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t n\u7919 a, l\u7847 n n\'e0y tr\u7903  v\u7873  n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec th\'ec c\u7889  g\u7855 ng c\'e1ch xa h\u7855 n ra, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7885 c v\'e0o.\cb1 \
