\f1\b0 \cf2 M\uc0\u7897 t tr\u7853 n gi\'f3 \u273 \'eam th\u7893 i t\u7899 i. Tr\'ean TV tr\u7853 n b\'f3ng \u273 \'e3 k\u7871 t th\'fac, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n \u273 \u7893 i k\'eanh, ca s\u297  nam n\u7919  tr\'ean s\'e2n kh\u7845 u \u273 ang h\'e1t c\'f9ng nhau: "... K\u7873  c\u7853 n nhau, anh v\'e0 em h\u7865 n \u432 \u7899 c tr\u259 m n\u259 m. N\u7871 u ai ch\'edn m\u432 \u417 i b\u7843 y tu\u7893 i ch\u7871 t, xin \u273 \u7907 i ba n\u259 m tr\'ean c\u7847 u N\u7841 i H\'e0...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i s\u7919 ng s\u7901 . C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u, l\u7841 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  \u273 u\u7893 i theo s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c kh\'f3c l\u7899 n ch\u7841 y v\'e0o s\'e2n nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y thi\u7871 u ni\'ean li\u7873 n ng\'e2y ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat ch\u7889 c r\u7891 i x\'f4ng t\u7899 i \'f4m ch\u7863 t \u273 \'f9i ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng. C\u7853 u bi\u7871 t ph\'e2n n\u7863 ng nh\u7865 , c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng tr\u7843 i qua l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7845 m l\u7841 nh, \'fd t\u7913  trong l\u7901 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u7853 u hi\u7875 u r\'f5. C\u7853 u nh\u7901  hai anh em h\u7885  gi\'fap \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873 , hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t sinh th\'eam chuy\u7879 n g\'ec l\'e0 t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hu\uc0\u7889 ng h\u7891  H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u361 ng n\'f3i r\u7845 t c\'f3 l\'fd. \u272 \'e3 nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\'e0m sao c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n ng\u432 \u7901 i kia kh\'f4ng thay \u273 \u7893 i, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u y h\u7879 t n\u259 m x\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong b\uc0\u7909 ng l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, nh\'ecn H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i: "Y\'ean t\'e2m, t\'f4i hi\u7875 u r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng s\uc0\u7899 m h\'f4m sau ph\u7843 i l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y d\u7885 n d\u7865 p xong \u273 i ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i m\'e3i kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. V\'ec l\u7901 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7853 n th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7847 n n\'e0y sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  g\u7863 p l\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kia. Suy ngh\u297  ng\u7893 n ngang, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a tr\u7903  v\u7873  m\'f9a xu\'e2n n\u259 m ch\'edn tu\u7893 i \u7845 y, c\u7853 u ng\'e2y ng\u7889 c theo m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i anh em h\u7885  \u273 i ch\u417 i, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 th\u7915 a d\u7883 p c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd li\u7873 n l\'e9n ch\u7841 y m\u7845 t, b\u7887  l\u7841 i c\u7853 u m\u7897 t m\'ecnh tr\'ean con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7841  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u273 i qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\'f2 m\u7851 m \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 i r\u7845 t l\'e2u r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c m\u7899 i th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u7853 u ch\u7841 y qua b\'ean \u273 \'f3 h\u7887 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, h\'f4 th\u7853 t to m\u7845 y l\u7847 n "Xin ch\'e0o", nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\u7899 i c\u7853 u. C\u7853 u nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'f9ng b\'e0n tay nho nh\u7887  v\u7895  v\u7895  l\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c xoay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i, tr\'ean m\u7863 t "H\u7855 n", ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u361  quan.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c quay ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7887  ch\u7841 y, nh\u432  con th\'fa nh\u7887  ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t ch\u7841 y b\u7915 a, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u432 \u7899 ng, l\'fac quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn th\u7917  l\u7841 i ho\u7843 ng s\u7907  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n th\u7913  kia v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\'e1m theo ph\'eda sau c\'e1ch c\u7853 u m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u x\'f4ng v\'e0o m\u7897 t s\'e2n nh\u7887  thanh t\u297 nh r\u7845 t kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t, trong s\'e2n c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u hoa, \u273 ang \u273 \'fang k\u7923  hoa n\u7903 , \u273 i m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 c\u7843 nh \u273 \u7865 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thi\uc0\u7871 u ni\'ean th\'e2n nh\u432  thanh ng\u7885 c tr\u432 \u7899 c gi\'f3, m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o s\u417  mi tr\u7855 ng, \u273 \u7913 ng d\u432 \u7899 i c\'e2y ng\u7885 c lan \u273 ang \u273 \u432 a tay h\'e1i m\u7897 t c\'e0nh hoa r\u7911  xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7917 ng s\u7889 t, c\u7889  \'fd \u273 i v\'f2ng sang b\'ean c\u7841 nh v\u7909 ng tr\u7897 m nh\'ecn m\u7863 t thi\u7871 u ni\'ean, sau khi x\'e1c nh\u7853 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i li\u7873 n b\u7845 t ch\u7845 p t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\'e0o t\u7899 i, \'f4m \u273 \'f9i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng g\'e0o kh\'f3c...\cb1 \
\cb3 Thi\'ean s\uc0\u432  th\u7871  gia nh\u432  Tr\'ec gia ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n s\u7889 ng \u7849 n kh\u7887 i th\u7871  gian, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec gia, Di\u7879 p gia v\'e0 H\u7913 a gia l\u7841 i \u7903  r\u7845 t g\u7847 n nhau, Tr\'ec gia nghi\'ean c\u7913 uThi\'ean \u273 \u7841 o, Di\u7879 p gia nghi\'ean tu Qu\u7927  \u273 \u7841 o, hai b\'ean g\u7847 n nhau c\u361 ng c\'f3 d\u7909 ng \'fd \u273 \u7875  cho \u273 \u7841 o \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng t\u432 \u417 ng h\u7895  c\'f3 l\u7907 i. V\u7873  sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t n\u417 i c\u7853 u x\'f4ng v\'e0o ch\'ednh l\'e0 bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n d\'e0nh cho con \'fat c\u7911 a gia ch\u7911  Di\u7879 p gia d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  d\u432 \u7905 ng b\u7879 nh, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u \'f4m ch\u7863 t kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\'e1i xe \u273 i, l\u7897  tr\'ecnh kh\'f4ng g\u7847 n, tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ba ng\u432 \u7901 i thay nhau l\'e1i xe. Tuy r\u7857 ng H\u7913 a H\'e2n ch\u7881  sinh sau H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y m\u7845 y ph\'fat, khi c\'f2n b\'e9 hai anh em \u273 \'e1nh nhau m\u7895 i ng\'e0y, nh\u432 ng gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y lu\'f4n r\u7845 t th\u432 \u417 ng em g\'e1i, bi\u7871 t r\'f5 H\u7913 a H\'e2n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u thua k\'e9m, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i kh\'f4ng cho c\'f4 thay phi\'ean l\'e1i xe m\'e0 ch\u7881  t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\'e1i l\'e2u h\u417 n, \u273 \u7875  H\u7913 a H\'e2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881  nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7843  \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'fai v\'f2ng v\'e8o l\'fac g\u7847 n \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7873 u do H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a gia k\u7923  th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng \u7903  n\u417 i r\u7915 ng n\'fai hoang vu m\'e0 \u7903  ngo\u7841 i \'f4 tr\'ean n\'fai th\'e0nh ph\u7889  M n\u7893 i danh ph\u7891 n th\u7883 nh, nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a c\'e1c lo\u7841 i tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p, kh\u7843  n\u259 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng t\'ecnh c\u7901  \u273 i v\'e0o ph\u7841 m vi gia t\u7897 c l\'e0 c\u7921 c th\u7845 p, m\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'fai n\'e0y ch\'ednh l\'e0 con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 i t\u7899 i H\u7913 a gia.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  c\u7917 a s\u7893  xe nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i, m\'e2y tr\u7855 ng s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 l\u432 \u7907 n l\u7901 , h\u7847 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 , tr\u432 \u7899 c sau c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 xe c\u7897  n\'e0o kh\'e1c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i \u7903  gh\u7871  ph\u7909  l\u7845 y di \u273 \u7897 ng ra xem, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'edn hi\u7879 u. M\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u cho th\u7845 y b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 c\'e1ch H\u7913 a gia kh\'f4ng c\'f2n xa, c\u361 ng c\'e1ch Tr\'ec gia v\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i kia c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\'ecn s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9 ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893 , kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 l\u7841 i nh\u7899  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\u259 m \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u \u273 \'f9i \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f3c, thi\u7871 u ni\'ean tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn ch\u7881  l\u7899 n h\u417 n c\u7853 u ch\u7915 ng b\u7889 n, n\u259 m tu\u7893 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, ch\u7881  b\u7871  c\u7853 u l\'ean \'f4m tr\'ean c\'e1nh tay, c\'f2n \u273 \u432 a c\'e0nh hoa lan v\u7915 a h\'e1i xu\u7889 ng cho c\u7853 u ch\u417 i. B\u7871  c\u7853 u v\'e0o nh\'e0 \u273 \u7863 t xu\u7889 ng sofa, l\u7841 i t\u7921  m\'ecnh c\u7847 m kh\u259 n \u7845 m lau m\u7863 t cho c\u7853 u, \u273 un s\u7919 a \u7845 m cho c\u7853 u u\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i m\uc0\u7865  ra ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f3 ai h\u7871 t l\'f2ng ch\u259 m s\'f3c c\u7853 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i b\u7883  h\'f9 s\u7907 , hai tay ng\u417  ng\'e1c \'f4m c\u7889 c th\u7911 y tinh l\u7899 n \u273 \u7921 ng s\u7919 a, ng\u7917 a \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn thi\u7871 u ni\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t. Ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u nh\u7887  \'f4m c\u7889 c l\u7899 n tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c, trong \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t to tr\'f2n \u273 en l\'e1y \'e1nh th\u7911 y quang, h\u7889 c m\u7855 t c\'f2n \u273 \u7887  h\u7891 ng, nh\'ecn v\u7915 a v\'f4 t\u7897 i v\u7915 a \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thi\uc0\u7871 u ni\'ean l\u7845 y c\u7889 c t\u7915  trong tay c\u7853 u \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean b\'e0n, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o l\'f2ng, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t m\u7873 m gi\u7885 ng d\u7895  d\'e0nh: "Ngoan, nh\'f3c \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng, n\'f3i cho ca ca bi\u7871 t, em t\'ean l\'e0 g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'f3n tay thi\uc0\u7871 u ni\'ean h\u417 i l\u7841 nh, nh\u432 ng v\'f2ng \'f4m l\u7841 i r\u7845 t \u7845 m \'e1p, c\'f3 kh\'ed t\u7913 c l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u7843 m th\u7845 y an t\'e2m. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c li\u7873 n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng d\u7921 a v\'e0o, m\u7873 m m\u7873 m n\u7857 m tr\'ean ng\u7921 c ng\u432 \u7901 i ta, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... Em t\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u g\u7889 i l\'ean l\u7891 ng ng\u7921 c ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , nghe ti\u7871 ng tim \u273 \u7853 p c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u v\'ec sao m\'e0 kh\'f3c l\'ean. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  cho l\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f2n s\u7907  h\'e3i, \'f4m \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  v\u7915 a n\'f3ng v\u7915 a m\u7873 m trong ng\u7921 c d\u7895  d\'e0nh r\u7891 i h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i tr\u7845 n an \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m \uc0\u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  l\u7841 i bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi cho c\u7853 u u\u7889 ng s\u7919 a, c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u259 n c\u417 m, k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n cho c\u7853 u nghe, n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t th\u7913  c\u7853 u g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kia ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t du h\u7891 n l\u7841 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, b\u7903 i v\'ec kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'ean ph\u7843 i \u273 u\u7893 i theo ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7875  \u273 i c\'f9ng, sau khi c\u7853 u \u273 i v\'e0o ph\u7841 m vi nh\'e0 n\'e0y th\u7913  kia kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 i theo n\u7919 a. \u272 \u7871 n t\u7889 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng ng\u7911  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i d\u7895  c\u7853 u ng\u7911 , nh\'ecn c\u7853 u ch\'ecm v\'e0o m\u7897 ng \u273 \u7865 p r\u7891 i m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 Tr\'ec gia t\u7899 i t\'ecm, \u273 \'f3n Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7873 . Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c t\'fai ph\'fac \u273 eo l\'ean c\u7893  c\u7853 u, trong t\'fai ch\u7913 a m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c ph\'f9 d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng hai chi\u7873 u, bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n c\'e1ch Tr\'ec gia kh\'f4ng xa, sau n\'e0y n\u7871 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean mu\u7889 n t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y th\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i theo ch\u7881  d\u7851 n c\u7911 a ph\'f9 d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, m\'e0 ch\u7881  c\u7847 n c\u7853 u \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i ra \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\'f2n nh\u7887  nh\u432 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7889 t x\u226 \u769 u, c\u7853 u \u7903  Tr\'ec gia kh\'f4ng h\u7841 nh ph\'fac, nh\u432 ng \u7903  trong bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n l\u7841 i tho\u7843 i m\'e1i d\u7877  ch\u7883 u, t\u7915  \u273 \'f3 v\u7873  sau h\u7847 u nh\u432  ng\'e0y n\'e0o c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n. Ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  Tr\'ec gia kh\'f4ng ai qu\u7843 n c\u7853 u, m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t con trai m\'ecnh s\u7889 ng \u7903  Tr\'ec gia kh\'f4ng vui, sau khi hi\u7875 u r\'f5 chuy\u7879 n c\u361 ng ng\u7847 m \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd vi\u7879 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean \u273 \u7871 n bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n. C\'e0ng v\u7873  sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng \u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \'f3 l\'e2u, th\u7853 m ch\'ed \u7903  t\u7853 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng, \u273 \u7871 n khi m\u7865  c\u7853 u cho ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u m\u7899 i l\u432 u luy\u7871 n kh\'f4ng th\'f4i m\'e0 r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'fac b\'e1 qu\uc0\u7843 n gia ph\u7909  tr\'e1ch s\u7921  v\u7909  \u7903  bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u r\u7845 t kinh ng\u7841 c, nh\u432 ng th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i tr\'f4i qua c\u361 ng d\u7847 n quen kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean n\u7919 a, \'97\'97 tr\u432 \u7899 c khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7871 n, \'f4ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  tr\u7901 i sinh t\'ednh t\'ecnh c\'f4 \u273 \u7897 c l\u7841 i th\'e2n thi\u7871 t v\u7899 i ai nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0 con c\u7911 a gia ch\u7911  Di\u7879 p gia khi tu\u7893 i \u273 \'e3 l\u7899 n, hai anh trai \u273 \u7873 u l\u7899 n h\u417 n h\u7855 n ch\u7915 ng hai m\u432 \u417 i tu\u7893 i, t\'ednh ra ngang h\'e0ng v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n. D\u7921 a theo vai v\u7871 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7889 n ph\u7843 i g\u7885 i h\u7855 n l\'e0 ch\'fa. Nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i c\u417  duy\'ean x\u7843 o h\u7907 p t\'ecnh c\u7901  g\u7863 p nhau nh\u432  v\u7853 y, tu\u7893 i l\u7841 i ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n g\u7885 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 ca ca.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7853 m r\'e3i nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, h\'ecnh b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  trong \u273 \u7847 u l\'fac xa l\'fac g\u7847 n, khi th\'ec r\'f5 r\'e0ng khi th\'ec m\u7901  nh\u7841 t, nh\u432 ng c\u7889  g\u7855 ng h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i, m\u7895 i c\u7917  ch\u7881  m\u7895 i n\'e9t m\u7863 t c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  li\u7873 n tr\u7903  n\'ean v\'f4 c\'f9ng ch\'e2n th\u7921 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  chuy\u7879 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'e1ch ra ch\u7881  l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe t\uc0\u7915  t\u7915  d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i. H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y th\'e1o d\'e2y an to\'e0n, c\u7845 t gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i r\u7891 i, xu\u7889 ng xe th\'f4i." Hai anh em mang Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7863 p cha m\u7865  b\u7885 n h\u7885  tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  n\'f3i g\'ec v\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7889 i, c\'f3 n\'f3i th\u7853 t r\u7857 ng ch\u7881  v\'ec mu\u7889 n gi\'fap Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'ean d\'f9ng th\'e2n ph\u7853 n b\u7841 n trai t\u7899 i tham gia L\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i hay kh\'f4ng hay l\'e0 b\u7883 a m\u7897 t c\'e2u chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c \u273 \u7875  h\u7885  c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n. T\'f3m l\u7841 i H\u7913 a nh\u7883  gia v\'e0 Nh\u7883  phu nh\'e2n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u "B\u7841 n trai" n\'e0y c\u7911 a con g\'e1i m\'ecnh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  hai \u273 \u7913 a con d\u7851 n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng v\u7873  nh\'e0 ch\u417 i, giao cho qu\u7843 n gia s\u7855 p x\u7871 p ph\'f2ng cho c\u7853 u, l\u7901 i n\'f3i vi\u7879 c l\'e0m \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng th\'e2n thi\u7871 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7841 nh nh\u7841 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u259 n c\u417 m, cha H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i con trai: "M\u432 \u7901 i ng\'e0y n\u7919 a L\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i s\u7869  b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u, ng\'e0y mai kh\'e1ch s\u7869  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7911 , nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y c\'e1c con \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cha h\uc0\u7855 n li\u7871 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\u7841 i n\'f3i: "T\u7889 i mai \u273 \u7875  hoan ngh\'eanh kh\'e1ch kh\u7913 a b\u7841 n b\'e8, trong t\u7897 c s\u7869  t\u7893  ch\u7913 c m\u7897 t b\u7919 a ti\u7879 c, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  t\u7853 p trung \u273 \'f4ng \u273 \u7911 , \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 hai \u273 \u7913 a mang Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec \u273 i c\'f9ng \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda H\u7913 a ph\u7909 , ng\u7915 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat tr\u7847 m gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ch\'e1u c\u7843 m \u417 n b\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a ph\u7909  kho\'e1t tay, n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u259 n c\u417 m, kh\'f4ng nh\u7855 c l\u7841 i \u273 \u7873  t\'e0i n\'e0y n\u7919 a. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 o\'e1n hai anh em H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y h\u7859 n l\'e0 kh\'f4ng g\u7841 t cha m\u7865  m\'ecnh, \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i h\u7871 t t\'ecnh h\'ecnh th\u7921 c t\u7871 , H\u7913 a ph\u7909  m\u7899 i c\u7889  \'fd nh\u7855 c m\u7897 t c\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7919 a ti\u7879 c t\u7893  ch\u7913 c ngay trong m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh c\u7911 a H\u7913 a gia, t\u7915  ch\u7895  \u7903  c\u7911 a H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 i kho\u7843 ng m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat. H\'f4m sau l\'fac ch\u7841 ng v\u7841 ng t\u7889 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y H\u7913 a H\'e2n xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t, H\u7913 a ph\u7909  H\u7913 a m\u7851 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 i t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng \u273 i c\'f9ng b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7901 i Tr\'ec gia \u273 \'e3 b\u7843 y, t\'e1m n\u259 m, d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 cao l\'ean, v\u7867  non n\u7899 t th\u7901 i ni\'ean thi\u7871 u \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y quen m\u7855 t nh\u432 ng nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra l\'e0 ai. L\'fac gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i r\'f5, ch\u7881  n\'f3i l\'e0 b\u7841 n trai c\u7911 a em g\'e1i, l\u7847 n n\'e0y v\u7873  nh\'e0 c\'f9ng H\u7913 a H\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y trong s\u432  m\'f4n m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng c\'f3 nguy\'ean t\u7855 c ng\u7847 m hi\u7875 u nhau, nghi l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p d\u7851 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng quan h\u7879  t\u7899 i tham gia, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u l\'e0 b\u7841 n trai c\u7911 a H\u7913 a ti\u7875 u th\u432  th\'ec kh\'e1c. Ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\'f9ng b\u7841 n g\'e1i v\u7873  nh\'e0, \u273 \u7841 o l\'fd hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean, n\u7871 u t\'ecnh c\u7843 m h\'f2a h\u7907 p ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng sau n\'e0y s\u7869  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t nh\'e0, n\u7871 u nh\'e0 trai b\u7857 ng l\'f2ng \u7903  r\u7875 , v\u7873  sau coi nh\u432  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a H\u7913 a gia, v\u7853 y c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \u7875  n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng con ch\'e1u h\u7853 u b\u7889 i H\u7913 a gia ng\u7891 i c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895 , v\u7883  tr\'ed g\u7847 n trong g\'f3c, kh\'f4ng thu h\'fat t\u7847 m m\u7855 t c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c. Ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i m\u7845 y anh em h\u7885  h\'e0ng c\u7911 a H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\u7841 i l\u7863 ng l\u7869  d\'f2 x\'e9t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nh\'ecn c\u7853 u r\u7845 t quen m\u7855 t, sau \u273 \'f3 nghe ng\'f3ng d\'f2 h\u7887 i t\'ean, nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7885  "Tr\'ec" \u273 \u7863 c th\'f9 li\u7873 n ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n Tr\'ec gia, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\u7899  ra c\u7853 u ch\'ednh l\'e0 ch\'e1u \u273 \'edch t\'f4n "t\'e1ch ra" t\u7915  Tr\'ec gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7891 i ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a c\'f9ng H\u7913 a H\'e2n v\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, l\u7863 ng l\u7869  \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, t\u7847 m m\u7855 t c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t ch\'fa \'fd \u273 \u7871 n v\u7883  tr\'ed ch\'ednh, kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \u273 \'e2u, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y cha m\'ecnh Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n. Nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i c\u7853 u m\'e0 v\u7851 n lu\'f4n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i \'f4ng n\u7897 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y. B\'ean c\u7841 nh h\u7885  c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7845 y ch\u7895  tr\u7889 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i b\'ean tr\'e1i t\u7893  ph\u7909  H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, nh\'ecn trong ph\'fat ch\u7889 c m\u7899 i d\u7901 i \'e1nh m\u7855 t qua ch\u7895  kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7855 c tr\u7901 i c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng t\u7889 i, tr\'ean b\'e0n ch\'ednh \u273 \'e3 k\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 v\u7883  tr\'ed kia c\'f2n tr\u7889 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\u432 u t\'e2m \u273 \u7897 ng th\'e1i h\u432 \u7899 ng kia, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y H\u7913 a l\'e3o gia t\u7917  ph\'e2n ph\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3 v\u7899 i \u273 \u7841 i qu\u7843 n gia c\u7911 a H\u7913 a gia, \u273 \u7841 i qu\u7843 n gia theo l\u7901 i lui ra. Kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u l\u7841 i b\u432 \u7899 c nhanh v\'e0o, n\'f3i nh\u7887  v\'e0i c\'e2u b\'ean tai H\u7913 a l\'e3o gia t\u7917 , ngay sau \u273 \'f3 t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean b\'e0n ch\'ednh \u273 \u7873 u xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7917 a ra v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f2n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng nh\'ecn theo ra c\u7917 a, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec \u273 \'f3, ch\'e2u \u273 \u7847 u gh\'e9 tai b\'e0n t\'e1n v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7897 i t\'e2m Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng tho\'e1ng c\'f3 d\u7921  c\u7843 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  nghe th\u7845 y ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng \'f4 t\'f4 d\u7915 ng xe, ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 hai c\'e1nh c\u7917 a g\u7895  c\u7911 a s\u7843 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\'e2n vi\'ean ph\u7909 c v\u7909  \u7903  b\'ean ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7849 y v\'e0o trong, nh\'e2n vi\'ean ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3n cung k\'ednh c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u khom ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7875  cho v\u7883  kh\'e1ch m\u7899 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t \u273 o\'e0n ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7889 i nhau v\'e0o, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i \u273 \u7847 u m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o cho\'e0ng d\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en, th\'e2n h\'ecnh cao g\u7847 y, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t tu\u7845 n m\u7929 , tr\'ean m\u7863 t l\u7841 i h\u417 i t\'e1i nh\u7907 t. \u272 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en s\'e2u th\u7859 m m\'e0 t\u297 nh m\u7883 ch, h\u417 i h\u7841  xu\u7889 ng t\u7921 a nh\u432  kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m m\u7885 i s\u7921 , \u273 \'f3n ti\u7871 p \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7911 a m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng nhanh kh\'f4ng ch\u7853 m \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c. R\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 ang \u273 \u7847 u xu\'e2n, theo h\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n, trong s\u7843 nh l\u7841 i d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  d\'e2ng l\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a l\'e3o gia t\u7917  \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i \u273 i t\u7899 i ngh\'eanh \u273 \'f3n, nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c tr\'ean b\'e0n c\u361 ng \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean theo. C\u7913  th\u7871  t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\'f4 h\u7845 p c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i. T\u7915  khi nam nh\'e2n \u273 i v\'e0o, \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  k\'ecm ch\u7871  m\'e0 d\'ednh tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tr\'ean th\u7871  gian n\'e0y ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kia. H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y v\'ec \u273 \u7875  tr\'e1nh cho c\u7853 u bi\u7875 u l\u7897  qu\'e1 kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng ho\u7863 c qu\'e1 m\u7913 c k\u7923  qu\'e1i, l\u7863 ng l\u7869  gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t tay \'e1o c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n c\'f9ng H\uc0\u7913 a l\'e3o gia t\u7917  h\'e0n huy\'ean hai c\'e2u, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y H\u7913 a l\'e3o gia t\u7917  c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua b\'ean tr\'e1i h\u7897 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh tr\u7903  l\u7841 i b\'e0n ch\'ednh m\u7901 i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng. M\'e0 nam nh\'e2n l\u7841 i kho\'e1t tay \'e1o v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i theo ph\'eda sau, quay b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n, m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u273 i th\u7859 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'ean tr\'e1i, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \'e1nh m\u7855 t y\'ean l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean "A" m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a r\u7891 i t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, l\'fac n\'e0y trong \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh ch\u7881  c\'f2n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng li\u7873 n \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t thu h\'fat \'e1nh m\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  th\u7845 y nam nh\'e2n h\u417 i c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i, tay tr\'e1i xoa nh\u7865  c\u7857 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean, kh\u7869  n\'e2ng l\'ean, \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 m\u7863 t m\'e0y ng\u361  quan c\u7853 u k\u7929  c\'e0ng, kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng hi\u7879 n l\'ean \u273 \u7897  cong nhu h\'f2a, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng n\'f3i: "V\'e0i n\u259 m kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p, A Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean \u273 \'e1p nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, nh\u7899  t\u7899 i l\u7901 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, v\'f4 th\u7913 c nh\'ecn sang ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean tr\'e1i. H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u361 ng \u273 ang nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, b\u7897  d\'e1ng b\'f3 tay kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean do d\uc0\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\'e2ng m\u7855 t nh\'ecn nam nh\'e2n, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: "V\'e2ng, Di\u7879 p gia ch\u7911  v\u7851 n kh\u7887 e ch\u7913 ?" C\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y g\u7885 i th\u7859 ng l\'e0 Di\u7879 p gia ch\u7911  th\'ec h\u417 i k\u7923  qu\'e1i, nh\u432 ng x\u432 ng h\'f4 ng\'e0y x\u432 a kh\'f4ng th\u7875  g\u7885 i, c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i x\u432 ng h\'f4 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n kh\uc0\u7869  nh\u7871 ch m\'f4i d\u432 \u7899 i, n\'e9t m\u7863 t gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u432 \u7901 i, hai m\u7855 t \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean g\u7885 i ta l\'e0 g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn \'e1nh m\uc0\u7855 t h\u7855 n, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'fd c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, ng\u7853 p ng\u7915 ng, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng g\u7885 i: "... Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n tho\'e1ng n\uc0\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i, l\u7847 n n\'e0y l\'e0 th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\u432 \u7901 i, to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e9t tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7903  n\'ean d\u7883 u d\'e0ng, kh\'f3e m\u7855 t \u273 u\'f4i l\'f4ng m\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \u7847 y ti\u7871 u \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  ch\u7907 t nh\u7853 n ra \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 n\u417 i t\u7889 t \u273 \u7875  \'f4n chuy\u7879 n, k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u k\u7873  s\'e1t m\'ecnh, gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "Ca ca nh\u7899  A Di\'ean, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i h\'f4m nay c\'f9ng ca ca tr\u7903  v\u7873 , \u273 \u7875  ca ca th\u432 \u417 ng em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Bi\uc0\u7871 t r\'f5 r\u7857 ng nam nh\'e2n lu\'f4n th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7853 u c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u, n\'f3i l\u7901 i n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd t\u7913  g\'ec kh\'e1c, ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7901 i c\u7853 u \u273 i \'f4n l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n c\u361 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t. C\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7917  ch\u7881  th\'e2n m\u7853 t nh\u432  th\u7871  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p l\u7855 m, d\'f9 sao c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 ti\u7875 u h\'e0i t\u7917 , Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca v\u7851 n \u273 \u7889 i x\u7917  v\u7899 i c\u7853 u nh\u432  \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  ch\u432 a d\u7913 t s\u7919 a n\u259 m x\u432 a, \'f4m \'f4m \u7845 p \u7845 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay c\uc0\u7853 u ch\u7889 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7849 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng ra m\u7897 t ch\'fat, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\u7905 , ch\u7881  duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng \u273 \'e1p: "V\'e2ng" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn gi\uc0\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\u7853 u thu\u7853 n theo m\'e0 ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng d\u7921 a v\'e0o ng\u7921 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
