\f1\b0 \cf2 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng s\'e1t nhau, nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f2n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nghe r\'f5 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang n\'f3i g\'ec, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y c\u7843  hai d\'e1ng v\u7867  th\'e2n m\u7853 t \u273 \u7913 ng chung m\u7897 t ch\u7895 . Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ai kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, d\'f9 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i khi\u7871 n H\u7913 a l\'e3o gia t\u7917  \u273 \'edch th\'e2n \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y ngh\'eanh \u273 \'f3n l\'e0 ai th\'ec ch\u7881  c\u7847 n h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh ho\u7863 c nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'ean b\'e0n ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'ec kh\'f4ng m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i r\'f5, h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7901 i quen bi\u7871 t H\u7913 a gia c\u361 ng ch\u7881  nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e1p \'e1n kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c: "H\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 b\u7841 n trai c\u7911 a ti\u7875 u th\u432  H\u7913 a gia d\u7851 n v\u7873  nh\'e0 ". D\'f9 mi\u7879 ng \u273 \'e1p v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng trong l\'f2ng c\u361 ng b\u7891 n ch\u7891 n, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i Nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u gia \u273 \'fang l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean kia l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a em g\'e1i, nh\u432 ng nh\'ecn b\u7897  d\'e1ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, c\u7853 u ta l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng \u273 \u7889 i t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a ti\u7875 u th\u432  H\u7913 a gia m\'e0 gi\u7889 ng ti\u7875 u t\'ecnh nh\'e2n c\u7911 a ch\u7911  nh\'e2n Di\u7879 p gia h\u417 n. Nh\u432 ng n\'f3i \u273 i c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i n\'f3i l\u7841 i, m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7871 n t\u7915  b\'ean ngo\'e0i, l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  quen th\'e2n v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c?\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m b\'e0n t\'e1n qu\'e1 m\u7913 c, ch\u7881  h\u7887 i \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n hai c\'e2u li\u7873 n th\'f4i, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\'f3 v\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7907 t nh\u7899  ra c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean kia h\'ecnh nh\u432  ch\'ednh l\'e0 v\u7883  ch\'e1u \u273 \'edch t\'f4n \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c. T\'ednh s\u417  qua tu\u7893 i, \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'e1u \u273 \'f3 h\u7859 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 l\u7899 n t\u7847 m n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, h\'e0i l\'f2ng "\u7914 m" r\u7891 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, l\u7841 i thu\u7853 n th\u7871  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  ai nh\u7853 n ra kh\u7869  h\'f4n l\'ean v\'e0nh tai c\u7853 u, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i thu tay v\u7873 , quay l\u7841 i ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i v\u7851 n \u273 \u7875  tr\u7889 ng cho h\u7855 n tr\'ean b\'e0n ch\'ednh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7889 t ho\u7843 ng ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, h\u7891 n v\'eda tr\'ean m\'e2y c\u7847 m \u273 \'f4i \u273 \u361 a trong tay, ngay c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng \'e1nh m\u7855 t t\'f2 m\'f2 nh\u432  c\'f3 nh\u432  kh\'f4ng t\u7915  kh\u7855 p n\u417 i lia \u273 \u7871 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7907 t c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t kh\'e1c, khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn v\u7873  h\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \'f3 \'97\'97 l\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung. H\u7855 n \u273 ang ng\u7891 i b\'ean b\'e0n Tr\'ec gia, l\'fac \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n \'e1nh m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n quay \u273 \u7847 u qua ch\u7895  kh\'e1c, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng \u273 \u7893 i t\u7847 m m\u7855 t, quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y d\'f9ng d\u432  quang nh\'ecn l\u432 \u7899 t qua m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m anh ch\u7883  em h\u7885  h\'e0ng nh\'e0 m\'ecnh tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i bi\u7875 u c\u7843 m ng\u7891 i quanh b\'e0n, ch\u7881  ch\u7881  *t\'f9ng th\u7917  qu\u7871  ng\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, m\'f3n c\u7853 u th\'edch nh\u7845 t n\'e0y."\cb1 \
