\cf2 \cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean hi\uc0\u7875 u \'fd h\u7855 n, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a, ch\u7881  th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng t\'e1n g\u7851 u m\u7897 t hai c\'e2u v\u7899 i hai anh em.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Vi\uc0\u7877 n S\u417 n thu h\u7871 t m\u7897 t m\'e0n v\u7915 a r\u7891 i v\'e0o m\u7855 t, b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng thanh s\u7855 c ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n x\'e3 giao. K\u7923  th\u7853 t t\u7915  l\'fac Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i qua, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean \'f4ng \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n ra \u273 \u7913 a con trai kia c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, song \'f4ng v\u7901  nh\u432  kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t v\u7851 n nh\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  c\u7843 m x\'fac, nh\u432 ng trong l\'f2ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh t\u297 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  ngo\'e0i m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean bi\u7871 t r\'f5 tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\'ecnh c\u7843 m gi\u7919 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  t\u7889 t nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, c\u361 ng d\u7863 n Tr\'ec Dung ch\'fa \'fd \u273 i\u7875 m \u7845 y, nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  h\u7855 n m\u7897 t s\u7889  vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7915 ng qu\'e1 h\u7845 p t\u7845 p, \'edt nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7915 ng l\u432 u l\u7841 i ch\u7913 ng c\u7913  c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta tra ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'e2y phi\u7873 n to\'e1i cho m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng th\u7921 c ra ch\'ednh \'f4ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m. \'d4ng ngh\u297  khi \u273 \'f3 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  l\'e0 con \'fat Di\u7879 p gia, tr\u7901 i sinh y\u7871 u nh\u432 \u7907 c nhi\u7873 u b\u7879 nh, m\u7897 t m\'ecnh d\u432 \u7905 ng b\u7879 nh trong bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n, tu\u7893 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, t\'e2m tr\'ed ch\u432 a \u273 \u7911  ch\'edn ch\u7855 n, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\'f4 \u273 \u417 n nh\'e0m ch\'e1n v\u7915 a v\u7863 n c\'f3 \u273 \u7891  ch\u417 i nh\u7887  qu\u7845 n qu\'edt l\'e0m h\u7855 n vui v\u7867  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t. M\'e0 b\'e2y gi\u7901  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0 ch\u7911  nh\'e2n Di\u7879 p gia, uy v\u7885 ng kh\'f3 d\'f2, xa c\'e1ch \u273 \u7841 m m\u7841 c, ai c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  th\'e2n c\u7853 n, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'e1ch ra nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m h\u7855 n c\u361 ng ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng quan t\'e2m t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, cho n\'ean ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 t\'ecnh ngh\u297 a qu\'e1 s\'e2u v\u7899 i \u273 \u7913 a con n\'e0y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. D\'f9 thu\u7903  ni\'ean thi\u7871 u c\'f3 v\'e0i ph\u7847 n giao t\'ecnh, n\u259 m th\'e1ng xa c\'e1ch kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p l\u7841 i th\'eam th\'e2n ph\u7853 n \u273 \u7883 a v\u7883  thay \u273 \u7893 i, v\'e0i ph\u7847 n giao t\'ecnh kia c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7859 ng c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 \'f4ng \u273 o\'e1n chuy\u7879 n li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n Tr\'ec gia ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c ch\u7911  nh\'e2n Di\u7879 p gia s\u7869  \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m, ch\u7881  v\'ec mu\u7889 n ph\'f2ng xa n\'ean m\u7899 i nh\u7855 c Tr\'ec Dung ph\u7843 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng h\'f4m nay t\'ecnh h\'ecnh l\u7841 i v\u432 \u7907 t qu\'e1 d\u7921  li\u7879 u c\u7911 a \'f4ng. Kh\'e1ch qu\'fd \u273 \'f4ng \u273 \u7911 , ngay c\u7843  \'f4ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i tr\'e0 tr\u7897 n \u273 i v\'e0o, v\u7853 y m\'e0 Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  v\u7915 a \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 i th\u7859 ng qua \u273 \'f3, th\u7847 n th\'e1i c\u7917  ch\u7881  th\'e2n m\u7853 t, hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\u7843 m t\'ecnh. Ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y \'f4ng li\u7873 n b\u7845 t an, nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n Tr\'ec Dung l\'e0m \'f4ng \u273 \u7873 u r\'f5, ch\u7881  l\'e0 gi\u7843  v\u7901  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, m\u7855 t nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t m\u7903  cho qua, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i xem ra v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  k\u297  Tr\'ec Dung, b\u7843 o n\'f3 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'ec chuy\u7879 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n m\'e0 tr\u7903  n\'ean v\u7897 i v\'e0ng. Tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean ph\u7843 i y\'ean l\u7863 ng theo d\'f5i m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng thi\u7871 u suy ngh\u297 .\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng sau H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y \u273 i v\u7879  sinh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7907 i m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat sau \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i t\'ecm h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7921 a v\'e0o lan can gi\'f3 l\'f9a \u7903  h\'e0nh lang b\'ean ngo\'e0i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i t\u7899 i, h\u417 i x\u7845 u h\u7893  n\'f3i: "Chuy\u7879 n kia... T\'f4i ch\'ednh l\'e0 kh\'f4ng ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, h\u7855 n v\u7915 a h\u7887 i t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p suy ngh\u297 . Xin l\u7895 i c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\uc0\u7879 c g\'ec." H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  n\'f3i, "T\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng n\'e0y. Ban \u273 \u7847 u t\'f4i l\'e0 s\u7907  h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u c\'f2n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng ngh\u297  c\'e1ch thu h\'fat s\u7921  ch\'fa \'fd c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, ch\u7885 c gi\u7853 n h\u7855 n, d\'f9 sao nh\u7919 ng n\u259 m qua v\u7883  kia v\u7851 n n\u7893 i danh kh\'f4ng th\'edch g\u7847 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng th\'edch ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c c\u7889  \'fd ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng ti\u7871 p c\u7853 n h\u7855 n. T\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i n\u7871 u c\u7853 u nghi\u7871 n r\u259 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng m\u7899 i l\'e0 c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i nghe H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, nh\u432 ng n\'f3i ti\u7871 p th\'ec v\u7883  kia h\'ecnh nh\u432  qu\u7843  th\u7921 c \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng. C\u7853 u th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng, l\'fac \'f4ng n\u7897 i t\'f4i \u273 i t\u7899 i ch\'e0o \u273 \'f3n m\u7863 t h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau c\u7843 m x\'fac, c\u7853 u v\u7915 a g\u7885 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u 'Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca' m\u7863 t h\u7855 n li\u7873 n nh\u432  s\u7855 p n\u7903  hoa, kh\'f4ng gi\u7843  b\u7897  n\u7893 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7867  mu\u7889 n gi\u7843  b\u7897 ." N\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n ph\u7847 n sau, trong gi\u7885 ng H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i th\'eam v\'e0i ph\u7847 n tr\'eau ch\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i m\u7855 ng h\u7855 n, b\u7873  ngo\'e0i gi\u7843  b\u7897  kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m, trong l\'f2ng k\u7923  th\u7853 t \u273 \'e3 v\'f4 c\'f9ng x\u7845 u h\u7893 , v\u7873  \u273 i\u7875 m trong ngo\'e0i b\u7845 t nh\u7845 t n\'e0y c\u7853 u gi\u7889 ng Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n. C\u7853 u cho l\'e0 \'e2m l\u432 \u7907 ng l\'fac c\u7853 u v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7911  nh\u7887  r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y v\u7851 n lu\'f4n ph\u7843 i ng\u7891 i im b\'ean c\u7841 nh \u273 \'e3 nghe th\u7845 y, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng H\u7913 a H\'e2n c\u361 ng nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7899 n th\u7871  n\'e0y c\'f2n g\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c l\'e0 "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca" ... c\'f2n b\u7883  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t bao nhi\'eau ng\u432 \u7901 i nghe th\u7845 y... Tr\'ec Di\'ean che m\u7863 t, \u273 i theo H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y v\'e0o \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  c\u7917 a c\u7853 u v\'f4 th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 a m\u7855 t nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'e0n ch\'ednh, ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai, ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y nh\'ecn theo \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch: "Di\u7879 p gia ch\u7911  c\u417  th\u7875  lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 e, r\u7845 t \'edt khi l\u7897  di\u7879 n b\'ean ngo\'e0i, d\'f9 xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e2u. B\u7919 a ti\u7879 c l\u7847 n n\'e0y h\u7855 n tham d\u7921  ch\u7855 c t\u7893  ph\u7909  t\'f4i kinh ng\u7841 c l\u7855 m, l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i n\u259 m n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c h\u7855 n ch\u7881  xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n v\'e0o ng\'e0y t\u7871  t\u7921  th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i \u273 i v\u7889 n \u273 ang c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao, r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i l\'e0 "Bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\'f9ng ca ca", k\u7871 t qu\u7843  ch\u432 a n\'f3i m\u7897 t l\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 i m\u7845 t. Nghe H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i v\u7853 y th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh lo l\u7855 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Vi\uc0\u7879 c c\u417  th\u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 e c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean bi\u7871 t r\'f5, khi c\'f2n nh\u7887  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t th\'edch qu\u7845 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n \u273 \'f2i h\u7887 i, \'f4m tay ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \u273 \u7911 , h\u7877  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  \u273 \'f2i Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca b\u7871 . C\'f3 m\u7897 t l\u7847 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7871  c\u7853 u ng\u7855 m hoa trong s\'e2n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, b\u7871  c\u7853 u ra ngo\'e0i \u273 i d\u7841 o m\u7897 t gi\u7901 , c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n, v\u7851 n \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7893  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u th\u7845 p h\u417 n ch\'fat so v\u7899 i b\u7841 n b\'e8 c\'f9ng l\u7913 a, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng nh\u7887 , nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng c\'f3 s\u7913 c n\u7863 ng. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t m\u7921 c chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t l\'fac tr\u7855 ng l\'fac xanh, hai m\u7855 t nh\u7855 m nghi\u7873 n, l\'f4ng mi kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng rung \u273 \u7897 ng, g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng th\u7903  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u7883  d\u7885 a s\u7907 , \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi b\'e1c s\u297  \u273 i r\u7891 i v\u7851 n n\u7857 m b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng \'f4m tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\'f3n tay b\'e0n tay \u273 \u7873 u l\u7841 nh nh\u432  b\u259 ng, kh\u7869  run. C\u7853 u \'f4m tay ph\u7843 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean b\u7909 ng m\'ecnh mu\u7889 n truy\u7873 n h\u417 i \u7845 m, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i n\u7919 a m\u7899 i n\u7857 m ng\u7911  c\u7841 nh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'fac b\'e1 b\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec chuy\u7879 n l\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 m\'e0 s\u7855 c m\u7863 t v\u7899 i c\u7853 u r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t. C\u7853 u v\u7915 a c\u7843 m gi\'e1c oan \u7913 c l\u7841 i v\u7915 a c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\'ecnh b\u7883  ph\u7841 t \u273 \'fang t\u7897 i, b\u7903 i v\'ec lo l\u7855 ng cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e0 l\'fac ng\u7911  r\u7891 i c\'f2n l\u7863 ng l\u7869  ch\u7843 y n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, h\'f4m sau t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i hai m\u7855 t \u273 \u7873 u s\u432 ng l\'ean. Trong l\'fac t\u7881 nh t\u7881 nh m\'ea m\'ea c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \'f4m c\u7853 u, h\'ecnh nh\u432  \u273 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Ph\'fac b\'e1: "Ng\'e0i \u273 \u7915 ng d\u7885 a A Di\'ean, A Di\'ean c\'f2n nh\u7887 , l\'e0 ta mu\u7889 n nu\'f4ng chi\u7873 u A Di\'ean nh\u432  v\u7853 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y thanh \'e2m c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  c\u7911 a Ph\'fac b\'e1: "Nh\u432 ng Tam gia \'e0, Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 h\'e0i t\u7917  nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta, ng\'e0i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  chi\u7873 u \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  m\'e3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tho\'e1ng ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, sau \u273 \'f3 kh\u7869  n\'f3i: "B\u7845 t lu\u7853 n l\'e0 con nh\'e0 ai, ta \u273 \u7873 u nu\'f4ng chi\u7873 u A Di\'ean c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f4i tay kia v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \u7897  \u7845 m nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7889 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh \u273 \'eam qua, kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\u7841 nh ng\u7855 t nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t. Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t b\'ean gi\u7843  b\u7897  ng\u7911 , m\u7897 t b\'ean l\u7863 ng l\u7869  ch\'f4n m\u7863 t trong l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\u7897 i t\'e2m v\u7915 a m\u7873 m v\u7915 a ng\u7885 t. C\u7849 n th\u7853 n ng\u7851 m l\u7841 i th\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  l\u7899 n h\u417 n c\u7853 u n\u259 m tu\u7893 i, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  anh hai trong nh\'e0 h\u7871 t m\u7921 c c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u, y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng t\u7915  \u273 \'f3 v\u7873  sau c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \'f2i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7871  c\u7853 u ra ngo\'e0i ch\u417 i n\u7919 a, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng mu\u7889 n b\u7871  c\u7853 u \u273 i, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  t\'ecm \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i l\'fd do c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t. V\u7873  sau l\u7899 n l\'ean r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n t\'ednh con n\'edt \u273 \u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m c\u7853 u b\'ean ngo\'e0i, song khi \u7903  trong bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7851 n g\u7847 n g\u361 i nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean h\'f4m nay th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m g\u7863 p l\u7841 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'e2n m\u7853 t k\u7873  s\'e1t m\'ecnh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7863 c d\'f9 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7907 ng ng\'f9ng v\u7899 i kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p v\'ec m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 ti\u7875 u h\'e0i t\u7917 , nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng v\'ec h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y k\u7923  l\u7841  \'97\'97 c\'f3 l\u7869  trong l\'f2ng Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, ch\'ednh m\'ecnh m\u7899 i m\'e3i l\'e0 \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  ch\u432 a l\u7899 n . H\u7855 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn c\u7853 u nh\u432  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh, c\'e0ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng sinh ra... t\'ecnh y\'eau v\'e0 d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921  v\u7899 i c\u7853 u. \cb1 \
\
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i, t\u7915  thu\u7903  m\u432 \u7901 i b\u7889 n m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m thanh xu\'e2n n\u7843 y m\u7847 m, ch\'ednh m\'ecnh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 d\'f9ng t\'ecnh c\u7843 m d\'e0nh cho ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh th\u7847 m m\u7871 n m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\'ecnh c\u7843 m \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i anh trai \u273 \u7875  y\'eau h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 ang l\'fac c\u7853 u ng\'e2y ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7845 t th\u7847 n \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  \u273 en \u273 i t\u7899 i ch\u7895  c\u7853 u, kh\u7869  khom ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'e0nh l\u7877 : "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, m\u7901 i ng\'e0i \u273 i theo t\'f4i, ch\u7911  nh\'e2n \u273 ang \u273 \u7907 i ng\'e0i tr\'ean xe."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn v\uc0\u7873  h\u432 \u7899 ng h\u7855 n n\'f3i, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u7903  g\'f3c r\u7869  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c xe \u273 ang \u273 \u7853 u, c\u7917 a s\u7893  gh\u7871  sau h\u7841  xu\u7889 ng m\u7897 t n\u7917 a, nh\u7901  \'e1nh s\'e1ng m\'e0u v\'e0ng \u7845 m \'e1p b\'ean trong c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\'f3ng d\'e1ng m\u7897 t nam nh\'e2n \u273 ang ng\u7891 i d\u7921 a tr\'ean l\u432 ng gh\u7871 . \cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7853 t gi\u7853 t y\u7871 t h\u7847 u, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y xua xua tay v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, \'fd b\u7843 o c\u7853 u \u273 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ca ca nh\uc0\u7899  A Di\'ean, t\u7889 i h\'f4m nay c\'f9ng ca ca tr\u7903  v\u7873 , \u273 \u7875  ca ca h\u7843 o h\u7843 o th\u432 \u417 ng em." Nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i vang l\'ean trong \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean, k\u7875  c\u7843  thanh \'e2m tr\u7847 m th\u7845 p r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u7911 a nam nh\'e2n , ng\u7919  kh\'ed v\u7915 a b\'ecnh th\u7843 n la\u803 i v\u7915 a \'e1i mu\u7897 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xong \uc0\u273 \u7901 i r\u7891 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, \u273 \u432 a tay che tr\'e1n. R\'f5 r\'e0ng g\u7847 n ngay tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, c\u7853 u l\u7841 i... c\'e0ng nh\u7899  h\u7855 n h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i theo ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng v\u7873  ph\'eda \'f4 t\'f4, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 \u273 \u7893  m\u7891  h\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng k\'e9o c\u7917 a sau xe, m\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i v\'e0o r\u7891 i l\u7841 i \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i b\'ean kia gh\u7871 , nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng li\u7873 n quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, v\u432 \u417 n tay c\u7847 m b\'e0n tay c\u7853 u \u273 ang \u273 \u7875  m\u7897 t b\'ean: "A Di\'ean c\'f3 l\u7841 nh kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e0n tay h\uc0\u7855 n thon d\'e0i, h\u7919 u l\u7921 c m\'e0 l\u7841 nh nh\u432  b\u259 ng, l\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c Tr\'ec Di\'ean quen thu\u7897 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7853 m r\'e3i l\u7841 i g\u7847 n, th\u7853 t c\u7849 n th\u7853 n th\u7845 p th\u7887 m nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n trong xe khi\u7871 n \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t s\'e2u \u273 en c\u7911 a h\u7855 n tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn v\'f4 c\'f9ng d\u7883 u d\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7897 ng c\u417  kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng, \'f4 t\'f4 nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng l\u259 n b\'e1nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  nhi\'ean kh\u7869  chuy\u7875 n t\u7847 m m\u7855 t, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca..."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, n\u7855 m \u273 \u7879 m l\'f4ng tr\'ean gh\u7871  ng\u7891 i: "A Di\'ean c\u361 ng nh\u7899  anh." C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c trong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh to\'e1t ra bao nhi\'eau \u7927  l\u7841 i v\'e0 \u7911 y khu\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ngoan." Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i du\u7895 i tay \'f4m c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7921 a v\'e0o vai h\u7855 n, "Ti\u7875 u b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, ca ca mang em v\u7873  nh\'e0."\cb1 \
