\f1\b0 \cf2 H\uc0\u7913 a gia \u273 \'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  n\u417 i \u7903  cho c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432  thu\u7853 t s\u297  \u273 \u7871 n tham gia l\u7877  t\u7871 , th\u7871  nh\u432 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i mang Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7873  th\u7859 ng Di\u7879 p gia. Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i v\u7873  bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n h\u7855 n d\u432 \u7905 ng b\u7879 nh n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 m\'e0 l\'e0 n\u417 i \u7903  c\u7911 a ch\u7911  nh\'e2n Di\u7879 p gia. Di\u7879 p gia v\'e0 H\u7913 a gia kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 g\u7847 n nhau nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng xa, \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  trong m\u7897 t khu v\u7921 c, l\'e1i xe ch\u7915 ng n\u7917 a gi\u7901  l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n. B\u7903 i v\'ec ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y n\'ean trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7853 u r\u7845 t \'edt t\u7899 i n\u417 i n\'e0y, c\'f3 v\'e0i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng l\'e0 c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec gia \u273 i tham gia m\u7845 y ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y s\uc0\u7855 c tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 t\u7889 i h\u7859 n, \'f4 t\'f4 ch\u7841 y th\u7859 ng m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn xuy\'ean qua c\u7917 a s\u7893  xe th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c khu nh\'e0 m\'e0u \u273 en v\'e0 \u273 \'e8n l\u7891 ng cam treo d\u432 \u7899 i m\'e1i hi\'ean, to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \u7841 i tr\u7841 ch Di\u7879 p gia \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao ph\u7911  trong y\'ean t\u297 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao kh\'f4ng th\uc0\u7845 y ai..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7849 m b\u7849 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sau khi hai anh trai c\uc0\u7911 a ta qua \u273 \u7901 i, ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng d\u7901 i kh\u7887 i *ch\u7911  tr\u7841 ch, nh\u7919 ng chi kh\'e1c c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y n\'ean r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u nh\'e0 b\u7887  kh\'f4ng." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\u7843 i th\'edch.\cb1 \
