\f1\b0 \cf2 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\'f2n ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o h\u432 \u7903 ng th\u7909 , m\u7863 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7921  m\'ecnh ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng, m\u7863 c c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 k\u7871 t c\u7845 u g\'ec m\'e0 d\'f9ng m\'f4i l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh "gi\'fap h\u7855 n l\'e0m \u7845 m". Nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  k\'ecm n\'e9n ch\u7889 c l\'e1t \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, l\u7853 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \'e1p Tr\'ec Di\'ean xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i th\'e2n h\'f4n c\u7853 u, sau m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u m\u7899 i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a th\u7887 a m\'e3n m\'e0 bu\'f4ng ra, th\u7903  g\u7845 p n\u7881  non: "... A Di\'ean c\u7911 a ta th\u7853 t ng\u7885 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\'e0ng \u273 \u7887  h\u417 n, m\u7903  to m\u7855 t kinh ng\u7841 c nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i \'e1p xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t kh\u7855 c t\u7915  \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  v\'e3n h\u7891 i, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'e2y d\u432 a h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i \'f4m nhau thi\u7871 p \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nh\u432  tr\u7903  v\u7873  thu\u7903  nh\u7887 , khi \u273 \'f3 \u7903  bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n c\u361 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t gian ph\'f2ng cho c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng qua \u273 \'eam \u7903  gian ph\'f2ng \u273 \'f3, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n ng\u7911  l\u7841 i bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n th\'ec c\u7853 u s\u7869  ng\u7911  c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi trong ph\'f2ng h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y th\u7853 t k\u7923  di\u7879 u, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\'e1ch bi\u7879 t nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m, c\u7843  hai \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u thay \u273 \u7893 i, nh\u432 ng sau khi g\u7863 p l\u7841 i l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  t\'e1ch ra, th\u7853 m ch\'ed v\'f2ng \'f4m c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\u361 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\'f4 c\'f9ng quen thu\u7897 c. L\u7901 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'fang, Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, r\'f5 r\'e0ng v\u7851 n l\'e0 Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'f4m ch\uc0\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh, trong \u273 \u7847 u m\u417  m\u417  h\u7891  h\u7891  m\'e0 h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i l\u7901 i \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i "... \u272 \'e0n \'f4ng con trai ph\u7843 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng s\u7869  b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta gi\'e0nh m\u7845 t" . Nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i s\u7861 n l\'f2ng v\u7899 i th\'e2n thi\u7871 t m\'ecnh \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 , v\u7853 y n\u7871 u m\'ecnh l\u7841 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng th\'eam ch\'fat n\u7919 a th\'ec s\u7869  \u273 o\u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ca ca th\'e0nh c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? Nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng c\u7853 u l\u7841 i h\u417 i kh\'f4ng t\u7921  tin, kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng n\'f3i nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i nh\u7909 t ch\'ed. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng nghe kh\'f4ng r\'f5 nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 g\'ec, c\u7913  dao \u273 \u7897 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y gi\u7919 a c\u7843 m x\'fac mu\u7889 n ng\'f3c \u273 \u7847 u d\u7853 y ti\u7871 n t\u7899 i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i gi\u7851 m ch\'e2n t\u7841 i ch\u7895  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n ng\u7911  say.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'fac n\uc0\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea c\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, \'e2m thanh t\u7915  ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a truy\u7873 n v\'e0o. Trong ph\'f2ng t\u7889 i \u273 en nh\u432  m\u7921 c, \u273 \'e8n \u273 \'e3 t\u7855 t t\u7915  l\'e2u, nh\u432 ng trong h\'e0nh lang \u273 \'e8n v\u7851 n s\'e1ng, m\u7897 t tia s\'e1ng xuy\'ean qua khe c\u7917 a, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\'f2n c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau v\'e0 ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n x\u7897 t xo\u7841 t truy\u7873 n v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nghe ra m\u7897 t gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 c\u7911 a Ph\'fac b\'e1: "... Tam gia, Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  s\u7855 p \u273 i r\u7891 i, ng\'e0i c\'f3 mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\'ecn m\u7897 t l\u7847 n kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f2n c\'f3 gi\uc0\u7885 ng n\'f3i l\u7841 nh nh\u7841 t c\u7911 a Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca: "Nh\'ecn g\'ec? A Di\'ean b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'f3 quan h\u7879  v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 nh\u7919 ng \'e2m thanh kia \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t. Nam nh\'e2n \u273 i v\'e0o, c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  b\u7883  \u273 \'f3ng r\u7891 i kh\'f3a l\u7841 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t b\'e0n tay l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o \'e1p l\'ean tr\'e1n, sau \u273 \'f3 t\u7915  tr\'e1n tr\u432 \u7907 t xu\u7889 ng. C\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'ed t\u7913 c l\u7841 nh nh\u432  b\u259 ng \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n, kh\'f3e m\u7855 t in xu\u7889 ng m\u7897 t n\u7909  h\'f4n l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n n\uc0\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh, k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7909 t v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng , ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ng\u7911 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Trong l\'f2ng l\uc0\u7841 i tho\'e1ng ch\'fat nghi ho\u7863 c v\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng. Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca b\'e2y gi\u7901  th\u7871  n\'e0o, l\u7847 n n\'e0y tr\u7903  v\u7873  ch\u432 a th\u7845 y ca ca ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh, nh\u432 ng c\u417  th\u7875  l\u7841 i l\u7841 nh h\u417 n, trong tr\'ed nh\u7899  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, cho d\'f9 khi ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh n\u7863 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ca ca c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 ...\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \'eam v\'f4 m\u7897 ng, s\'e1ng h\'f4m sau t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tinh th\u7847 n th\u432  th\'e1i. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n nh\u432  \u273 \'eam qua ng\u7891 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh l\u7853 t s\'e1ch \u273 \u7885 c, th\u7845 y c\u7853 u t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n l\'ean mi m\u7855 t c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean mau d\u7853 y r\u7917 a m\u7863 t, c\'f2n kh\'f4ng d\u7853 y b\u7919 a s\'e1ng s\u7869  ngu\u7897 i m\u7845 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'e1o h\uc0\u7843 i s\u7843 n th\u417 m ngon, h\u432 \u417 ng b\'e1nh bao nh\'e2n g\u7841 ch cua x\'f4ng v\'e0o m\u361 i, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\'f3n Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'edch \u259 n, v\u7915 a n\u7871 m l\'e0 bi\u7871 t do Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\'e0m. C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7901 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\'fac n\'e0o chu\u7849 n b\u7883  b\u7919 a s\'e1ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean khi c\'f2n nh\u7887  kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n, th\'edch \u259 n nh\u7919 ng m\'f3n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m, th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean l\'e0m n\u361 ng \u273 \'f2i h\u7855 n n\u7845 u, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 au l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\u7899 n l\'ean h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i n\u7897 i t\'e2m c\'e0ng th\'eam chua x\'f3t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca ngh\uc0\u7881  ng\u417 i nhi\u7873 u ch\'fat, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n n\u7845 u cho em \u273 \'e2u." \u7902  trong b\u7871 p b\u7853 n r\u7897 n m\u7897 t l\'fac \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t hai gi\u7901 , c\u7853 u s\u7907  c\u417  th\u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng vi\uc0\u7879 c g\'ec," Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t b\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, " \u7902  l\u7841 i c\'f9ng ca ca, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y ca ca \u273 \u7873 u n\u7845 u cho A Di\'ean \u259 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e ca ca th\u7871  n\'e0o? T\u7889 t h\u417 n ch\'fat n\'e0o ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u7914 m." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7847 m ng\'e2m m\u7897 t ch\'fat, c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i, "V\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361 , duy tr\'ec nh\u432  v\u7853 y, d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7871 t ngay \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n c\'e0ng t\u7887  v\u7867  kh\'f4ng h\u7873  g\'ec nh\u432  v\u7853 y, trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y s\u7869  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i c\u7853 u, s\u7869  bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t kh\u7887 i th\u7871  gian, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  g\u7863 p l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sau n\'e0y kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p n\uc0\u7845 u c\u417 m n\u7919 a." Ng\u7919  kh\'ed kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 tr\u7903  n\'ean c\u7913 ng r\u7855 n .\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7881  n\u7845 u c\u417 m th\'ec th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec..." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'e2ng m\u7855 t nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7845 y \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t h\u417 i \u273 \u7887  l\'ean c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7899 i d\u7915 ng \u273 \u7873  t\'e0i n\'e0y l\u7841 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng m\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 , b\'e8n \u273 \u7893 i ch\u7911  \u273 \u7873  kh\'e1c, "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 \'eam qua A Di\'ean ng\u7911  th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "R\uc0\u7845 t t\u7889 t." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7915 a r\u7891 i m\'ecnh ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng h\u417 i qu\'e1, th\u7847 m ngh\u297  sau n\'e0y ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7875  m\u7855 t \u273 \u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng cho h\u7855 n l\'e0m nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c ph\'ed c\'f4ng t\u7889 n s\u7913 c, t\u297 nh d\u432 \u7905 ng cho t\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n t\u7889 i qua c\u7853 u l\u7841 i nh\u7899  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n: "N\u7917 a \u273 \'eam qua l\'fac t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, h\'ecnh nh\u432  em nghe th\u7845 y... t\u7893  ph\u7909  em \u273 \'e3 qua \u273 \u7901 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t \u273 \'fang nh\u432  l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i \u273 \'eam qua m\'e0 c\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u v\'e0 Tr\'ec gia \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n quan h\u7879 , c\u7853 u v\'e0 Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m g\'ec, n\u7871 u n\'f3i th\u7853 t l\'f2ng th\'ec, v\u7889 n ban \u273 \u7847 u c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7845 y ph\u7847 n o\'e1n kh\'ed, sau khi ra kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia ngay c\u7843  o\'e1n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 l\u432 \u7901 i o\'e1n, ch\u7881  coi \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i xa l\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kinh ng\u7841 c: "Qua \u273 \u7901 i? A Di\'ean nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u? Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  v\u7851 n kho\u7867  m\u7841 nh, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 ang b\u7871  quan tu h\'e0nh, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  g\u7863 p m\u7863 t. N\u7871 u em kh\'f4ng y\'ean l\'f2ng th\'ec ta c\'f3 th\u7875  mang em quay v\u7873  Tr\'ec gia th\u259 m m\u7897 t l\u7847 n."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng \u273 \'eam qua em nghe th\u7845 y ca ca v\'e0 Ph\'fac b\'e1 n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n... Em nghe th\u7845 y Ph\'fac b\'e1 n\'f3i 'Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  s\u7855 p kh\'f4ng c\'f2n", c\'f2n nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i em n\u7919 a." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat nghi ho\u7863 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em nghe l\uc0\u7847 m r\u7891 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi y\'ean l\u7863 ng n\'f3i, "Ph\'fac b\'e1 \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u432 a thu\u7889 c cho ta, l\u7901 i \'f4ng \u7845 y n\'f3i l\'e0 'Thu\u7889 c s\u7855 p kh\'f4ng c\'f2n."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7897 i t\'e2m Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n h\u417 i do d\u7921 , nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\'f4 c\'f9ng b\'ecnh th\u7843 n, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7841 m th\u7901 i \u273 \'e8 nghi v\u7845 n xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u258 n s\'e1ng xong t\'e0i x\u7871  h\'f4m qua l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay v\u7873  H\u7913 a gia, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  tr\u7903  l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c gi\u7901  \u259 n t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t m\'ecnh tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a s\u7893  \u273 \u432 a m\u7855 t nh\'ecn xe h\u417 i m\'e0u \u273 en d\u7847 n ch\u7841 y xa, kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\uc0\u7889 t cu\u7897 c, A Di\'ean c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 l\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  b\'ean h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n quay ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \u432 a tay kh\u7869  vu\u7889 t v\u7883  tr\'ed \u273 \'eam qua Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7857 m, h\'edp m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 A Di\'ean n\'f3i th\'edch h\uc0\u7855 n, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng h\'f4n h\u7855 n. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ngh\u297  t\u7899 i h\'ecnh \u7843 nh \u273 \'eam qua d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7857 m \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y b\u7883  h\u7855 n h\'f4n, m\u7863 t \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t s\'e1ng l\u7845 p l\'e1nh m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng h\u417 i n\u432 \u7899 c, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\'fa c\u432 ng nu\'f4i trong nh\'e0 kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n xa r\u7901 i m\'e0 nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, nh\'ecn \u273 \u7871 n l\'f2ng h\u7855 n m\u7873 m ra, l\u7841 i ng\u7913 a, h\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  b\u7855 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng v\'e0o l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay \u273 \'f9a ngh\u7883 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng l\'e0 h\'f4n, nh\u432 ng \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 \u7903  mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na A Di\'ean ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 A Di\'ean c\uc0\u7911 a h\u7855 n ng\u7889 c. Th\u7871  nh\u432 ng d\'f9 c\'f3 ng\u7889 c, tr\u7843 i qua x\'e3 h\u7897 i ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t h\'f4n l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec sao? C\u7853 u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t g\u7847 n g\u361 i m\'e0 th\'e2n m\u7853 t h\'f4n nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'e0 c\'f3 ngh\u297 a g\'ec sao? Nh\'ecn ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng khi \u7903  mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na, r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i, ch\'ednh l\'e0 gi\u7843  b\u7897  \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7889  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n d\u7909  ho\u7863 c m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  tr\'e1i tim Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432  tr\'f4i l\u417  l\u7917 ng, v\u7915 a ngh\u297  t\u7899 i khi \u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i trong l\u7901 i A Di\'ean c\u7911 a h\u7855 n nghi\'eam t\'fac n\'f3i "T\'f4i \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i trong l\'f2ng" ch\'ednh l\'e0 n\'f3i m\'ecnh, d\'f9 ch\u7881  l\'e0 kha\u777  n\u259 ng l\'e0 v\u7853 y... H\u7855 n nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  t\'e2m t\u432  xao \u273 \u7897 ng nh\u432  say r\u432 \u7907 u. N\u7871 u l\'e0 ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\'f3 l\u7869  h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t c\'e1i, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n b\'ecnh t\u297 nh l\u7841 i. Ti\u7875 u h\u7895 n \u273 \u7843 n, A Di\'ean ng\u7889 c, ca ca s\u7869  ch\u7901 , ch\u7901  xem em \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7915 a \u273 \u7871 n H\u7913 a gia nh\'ecn th\u7845 y H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c v\u7851 n nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'f2 h\u7887 i: "\u272 \'eam qua Tr\'ec gia kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t sinh chuy\u7879 n g\'ec ch\u7913 ? T\u7893  ph\u7909  t\'f4i b\'ean \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  th\u7853 t s\u7921  qua \u273 \u7901 i, cho d\'f9 l\'e0 b\u7879 nh t\'ecnh nguy k\u7883 ch, tin t\u7913 c \u273 \'f3 nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  truy\u7873 n t\u7899 i, m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u361 ng s\u7869  nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  gi\u7845 u gi\u7871 m n\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y ng\u7901  v\u7921 c c\'e2u h\u7887 i \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n suy ngh\u297  n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y tin g\'ec h\u7871 t. C\'f3 ai n\'f3i g\'ec v\u7899 i c\u7853 u \'e0?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\uc0\u7889 i qua h\'ecnh nh\u432  t\'f4i nghe c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i t\u7893  ph\u7909  t\'f4i s\u7855 p kh\'f4ng c\'f2n, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\u7845 t th\u7853 t, nh\u432 ng Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca b\u7843 o l\'e0 t\'f4i nghe l\u7847 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u416  k\'eca, l\u7841 i c\'f2n Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca." H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y tr\'eau ch\u7885 c c\u7853 u, "V\u7853 y nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 c\u7853 u nghe l\u7847 m r\u7891 i, chuy\u7879 n l\u7899 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tin t\u7913 c, h\u417 n n\u7919 a Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  v\u7851 n kh\u7887 e m\u7841 nh l\u7855 m, d\u7841 o n\'e0y c\'f2n \u273 ang b\u7871  quan, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng \u273 \u7897 t ng\u7897 t qua \u273 \u7901 i. C\u7853 u \u7845 y, Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, h\'f4m qua c\u7853 u v\u7899 i Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca c\u7911 a c\u7853 u ph\'e1t sinh chuy\u7879 n g\'ec r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f2n c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, ch\u7881  \'f4n l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n c\u361  th\'f4i." C\u7853 u ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n n\u7909  h\'f4n \u273 \'eam qua, trong l\'f2ng li\u7873 n nh\u7897 t, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \'e1p qua loa cho xong chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e1t sau H\u7913 a H\'e2n c\u361 ng \u273 \u7871 n t\'ecm, ba ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'e0n huy\'ean n\u7917 a ng\'e0y, v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng b\'e1c H\u7913 a \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 vi\u7879 c \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a ch\u7881  c\'f3 ba ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng nhau \u259 n c\u417 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai anh em H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y m\u432 \u7907 n c\u417  h\u7897 i mu\u7889 n tr\'eau ch\u7885 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0i c\'e2u, th\u7853 t s\u7921  b\u7885 n h\u7885  th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 l\u7899 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, g\u7863 p Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e2u "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca" hai c\'e2u "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca", s\u7889 ng ch\u7871 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7893 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mi\u7879 ng, r\u7845 t bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a H\'e2n n\'f3i: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, c\u7853 u n\'f3i xem sau n\'e0y t\'f4i ph\u7843 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t b\u7841 n b\'e8 h\u7885  h\'e0ng th\u7871  n\'e0o h\u7843 ? Tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t bao nhi\'eau ng\u432 \u7901 i, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u th\u7845 y, b\u7841 n trai t\'f4i d\u7851 n v\u7873  v\u7915 a g\u7863 p m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 \'e3 h\u7845 p d\u7851 n s\u7921  ch\'fa \'fd c\u7911 a ch\u7911  nh\'e2n Di\u7879 p gia, r\u7891 i \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 l\'ean xe Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , c\u7843  \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng v\u7873 , m\'e3i h\'f4m sau m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c xe c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p gia \u273 \u432 a v\u7873  H\u7913 a gia. C\u7853 u n\'f3i xem ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2y? Sau n\'e0y t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 t t\'f4i b\u7883  Di\u7879 p tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  \u273 \'e0o ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7901 ng."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (\uc0\u273 \'e0o ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7901 ng: n\'f4m na l\'e0 chen v\'e0o r\u7891 i n\u7851 ng m\u7845 t)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y tr\'eau gh\u7865 o em g\'e1i n\'f3i : "M\'e0y th\'ec thi\u7879 t c\'e1i g\'ec, c\u7841 nh tranh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7899 i ch\u7911  Di\u7879 p gia \'e0, c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f4ng m\'e0 \u273 \'f2i c\u7841 nh tranh."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7889 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u273 \'f9a gi\u7905 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i ch\u7897 t d\u7841 , ch\u7881  nghe m\'e0 m\u7863 t \u273 \u7887  t\u7899 i mang tai. C\u7853 u d\'e1m th\u7859 ng th\u7855 n bi\u7879 n b\u7841 ch v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh v\'e0 anh em H\u7913 a gia ch\u7881  l\'e0 b\u7841 n b\'e8 b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i m\'ecnh v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  l\'e0 t\'ecnh huynh \u273 \u7879  v\u7899 i anh em H\u7913 a gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 ang l\'fac ba ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i gi\u7905 n, qu\u7843 n gia nh\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y b\'e1o m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n, nh\'ecn H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y r\u7891 i nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, xong l\u7841 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, do d\u7921  \u273 \u7907 i ch\u7881  th\u7883  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y h\u7887 i \'f4ng: "C\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia n\'f3i: "L\'e0 vi\u7879 c v\u7873  L\'e2m Tr\u7909  con c\u7911 a L\'e2m Nh\u7883  t\u7849 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y ph\u7849 y tay: "Kh\'f4ng vi\u7879 c g\'ec, \'f4ng c\u7913  n\'f3i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean m\uc0\u7863 t qu\u7843 n gia hi\u7879 n l\'ean n\'e9t k\u7923  qu\'e1i, t\u7921 a h\u7891  \u273 ang c\'e2n nh\u7855 c v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  n\'e0y n\'ean n\'f3i th\u7871  n\'e0o, l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  hai gi\'e2y cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng n\'f3i: "V\u7915 a r\u7891 i L\'e2m Tr\u7909  \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'ecm th\u7845 y, kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7889 ng, thi th\u7875  \u7903  c\'e1nh r\u7915 ng trong n\'fai. \u272 \u7841 i qu\u7843 n gia \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n xem th\u7917 , nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 n\'f3i thi th\u7875  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t t\u7915  ba ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Sao c\'f3 th\uc0\u7875 ." H\u7913 a H\'e2n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, nh\'edu m\'e0y n\'f3i, "Khuya h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i c\'f2n tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y h\u7855 n m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean th\uc0\u7921 c t\u7871 , h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh H\u7913 a H\'e2n tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y L\'e2m Tr\u7909 .\
