\f1\b0 \cf2 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y l\'e0 qu\u7843 n gia nh\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, m\'e0 \u273 \u7841 i qu\u7843 n gia trong l\u7901 i \'f4ng l\'e0 \u273 \u7841 i qu\u7843 n s\u7921  c\u7911 a to\'e0n b\u7897  H\u7913 a gia, h\u7847 u h\u7841  H\u7913 a l\'e3o gia t\u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y nghe tin xong theo qu\u7843 n gia \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, c\'f2n l\u7841 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 H\u7913 a H\'e2n trong ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nghi ho\u7863 c, quay \u273 \u7847 u h\u7887 i H\u7913 a H\'e2n: "Chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y l\'e0 th\u7871  n\'e0o? Sao qu\u7843 n gia n\'f3i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t t\u7915  ba ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 c\u7853 u l\u7841 i n\'f3i \u273 \'eam tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f2n th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3? Ai th\u7871 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e2m Nh\uc0\u7883  t\u7849 u l\'e0 b\'e0 con xa nh\'e0 b\u7885 n t\'f4i, ch\u7891 ng b\'e0 \u7845 y m\u7845 t s\u7899 m, m\u7897 t m\'ecnh b\'e0 nu\'f4i con trai, gi\'fap vi\u7879 c l\u7863 t v\u7863 t trong t\u7897 c, khi t\'f4i c\'f2n nh\u7887  b\'e0 \u7845 y t\u7915 ng ch\u259 m s\'f3c hai anh em t\'f4i m\u7845 y ng\'e0y, v\u7873  sau L\'e2m Tr\u7909  \'96 con trai b\'e0 tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh th\'ec \u7903  trong t\u7897 c gi\'fap ph\u7909  vi\u7879 c lu\'f4n, m\u7845 y ng\'e0y t\u7871  l\u7877  n\'e0y c\u7853 u ta v\u7851 n gi\'fap \u273 \u7841 i qu\u7843 n gia ch\u7883 u tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m mua \u273 \u7891  v\'e0 ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3n c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432  t\u7899 i tham gia, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  t\u7915  s\'e1ng nay kh\'f4ng ai tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u7845 y. B\u7903 i v\'ec t\u7915 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c L\'e2m Nh\u7883  t\u7849 u ch\u259 m s\'f3c n\'ean hai anh em b\u7885 n t\'f4i coi nh\u432  c\u361 ng quen thu\u7897 c, d\u7863 n qu\u7843 n gia l\u432 u t\'e2m tin t\u7913 c v\u7873  c\u7853 u \u7845 y, t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec tr\u7903  l\u7841 i n\'f3i cho b\u7885 n t\'f4i bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng. Kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng l\u7841 i th\'e0nh ra th\u7871  n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y c\'f4 l\u7841 i nh\'edu m\'e0y: "Nh\u432 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng h\u7907 p l\'fd, khuya h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i th\u7921 c s\u7921  \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y L\'e2m Tr\u7909 , c\u7853 u \u7845 y c\'f2n h\u7887 i t\'f4i s\u7889 ng b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\'f3 t\u7889 t kh\'f4ng, n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i t\'f4i m\u7897 t l\'fac. C\u7843  ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua t\u7909 i m\'ecnh \u7903  c\'f9ng nhau, tuy kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p c\u7853 u \u7845 y nh\u432 ng \u273 \'eam qua c\'f3 ti\u7879 c, L\'e2m Tr\u7909  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\u7853 n r\u7897 n tr\'f9 b\u7883  s\u7855 p x\u7871 p ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i cho kh\'e1ch m\u7899 i \u273 \u7871 n. R\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  H\u7913 a gia tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u7845 y. Sau khi c\u7853 u \u7845 y m\u7845 t t\'edch c\u361 ng c\'f3 kh\'f4ng \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i \u273 \'eam qua \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u7845 y d\u7885 n ti\u7879 c t\'e0n xong m\u7899 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng. N\u417 i n\'e0y nhi\u7873 u thi\'ean s\u432  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, sao c\'f3 th\u7875  ngay c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i hay qu\u7927  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 n m\u7897 t gi\u7901  sau H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, n\'f3i cho b\u7885 n h\u7885  bi\u7871 t thi th\u7875  \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'fang l\'e0 L\'e2m Tr\u7909 , c\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng thi th\u7875  c\u361 ng nh\u7853 n \u273 \u7883 nh th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t ba ng\'e0y tr\u7903  l\'ean. Nh\u432 ng L\'e2m Tr\u7909  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t t\u7915  l\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, cho n\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7843 i th\'edch l\'e0 do y\u7871 u t\u7889  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 ho\u7863 c th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 trong r\u7915 ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7849 y nhanh qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh th\u7889 i r\u7919 a c\u7911 a thi th\u7875 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e3 th\u7917  chi\'eau h\u7891 n ch\u432 a anh?" H\u7913 a H\'e2n h\u7887 i. Ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7899 i \u273 i kh\'f4ng l\'e2u, \u273 \'e2y l\u7841 i l\'e0 n\u417 i L\'e2m Tr\u7909  s\u7889 ng t\u7915  nh\u7887 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 ch\u7871 t, theo l\'fd m\'e0 n\'f3i s\u7869  d\u7877  chi\'eau h\u7891 n, \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o ch\u7881  c\u7847 n h\u7887 i l\'e0 bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Chi\'eau r\uc0\u7891 i." H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i, "\u272 \u7841 i b\'e1 \u273 i, ban \u273 \u7847 u l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a B\'e0ng gia chi\'eau, th\u7917  ba l\u432 \u7907 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7841 i b\'e1 t\u7921  m\'ecnh chi\'eau h\u7891 n, kh\'f4ng chi\'eau \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, d\'f9ng c\u7901  d\u7851 n h\u7891 n c\u361 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 "D\'f9ng c\uc0\u7901  d\u7851 n h\u7891 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c?" H\u7913 a H\'e2n n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "\u7914 . Nh\u432 ng th\'f4i, \u273 \u7915 ng suy ngh\u297  n\u7919 a, \u273 \u7841 i b\'e1 \u273 \'e3 cho ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i \u273 i\u7873 u tra r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7901  d\u7851 n h\u7891 n l\'e0 ph\'e1p kh\'ed gia truy\u7873 n c\u7911 a H\u7913 a gia, c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  trong vi\u7879 c d\u7851 n h\u7891 n chi\'eau h\u7891 n, d\'f9 l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p n\u7871 u d\'f9ng c\u7901  d\u7851 n h\u7891 n c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  chi\'eau h\u7891 n th\'e0nh c\'f4ng, hu\u7889 ng chi l\'e0 \u273 \u7841 i b\'e1 nh\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y. M\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  v\'e3ng sinh nhanh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p n\'e0y ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai kh\u7843  n\u259 ng, m\u7897 t l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 khu\u7845 t kh\'f4ng c\'f2n v\u432 \u417 ng v\u7845 n g\'ec v\u7899 i th\u7871  gian, \u273 \'e3 nhanh ch\'f3ng v\'e3ng sinh, hai l\'e0 b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u432 u h\u7841 i, ngay c\u7843  h\u7891 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n. Tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p c\u7911 a L\'e2m Tr\u7909 , hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean lo\u7841 i th\u7913  hai c\'f3 kha\u777  n\u259 ng h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec vi\uc0\u7879 c n\'e0y m\'e0 b\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed \u7903  H\u7913 a gia, k\u7875  c\u7843  gi\u7919 a hai anh em H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 ph\u7847 n n\u7863 ng n\u7873 , th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m xe Di\u7879 p gia xe t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n Tr\'ec Di\'ean, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u361 ng ch\u7881  gi\'fap c\u7853 u x\'e1ch \u273 \u7891 , d\u7863 n d\'f2 c\u7853 u t\u7921  ch\u259 m s\'f3c b\u7843 n th\'e2n cho t\u7889 t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng c\'f2n t\'e2m t\u432  \u273 i tr\'eau ch\u7885 c c\u7853 u v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tr\uc0\u7903  l\u7841 i Di\u7879 p gia, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 b\'e0y s\u7861 n m\u7897 t b\'e0n c\u417 m ch\u7901  c\u7853 u, tr\'ean b\'e0n th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'ecnh r\u432 \u7907 u \u273 \u7871 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean thu d\uc0\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  xong ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, n\u7871 m th\u7917  m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng, bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i do Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m tho\'e1ng an t\'e2m, ngay sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\'f3t r\u432 \u7907 u cho hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c n\'f3ng n\u7843 y: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, ca c\'f2n u\u7889 ng r\u432 \u7907 u \u432 ?" C\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 tr\u432 \u7899 c kia nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  nh\u432  r\u432 \u7907 u, thu\u7889 c l\'e1, \u273 \u7891  \u259 n s\u7889 ng l\u7841 nh chua cay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7873 u ph\u7843 i ki\'eang.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat kh\'f4ng sao, th\u7847 y thu\u7889 c n\'f3i c\'f2n t\u7889 t cho s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e. H\u417 n n\u7919 a u\u7889 ng xong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u361 ng \u7845 m h\u417 n." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7845 t t\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 gi\u7843 i th\'edch. Nh\u432 ng trong \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec chuy\u7875 n \'fd ngh\u297  kh\'e1c, A Di\'ean gan nh\u7887  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\u7841 i ng\u7889 c, kh\'f4ng hu\'fdch c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i th\'ec e l\'e0 s\u7869  ch\u7881  d\'e1m gi\u7843  b\u7897  ng\'e2y ng\'f4 li\u7871 m li\u7871 m m\'ecnh, th\u7853 t s\u7921  h\'f4n th\'ec kh\'f4ng. Ph\u7843 i cho c\u7853 u u\u7889 ng ch\'fat r\u432 \u7907 u \u273 \u7875  t\u259 ng th\'eam d\u361 ng kh\'ed.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\'e1n t\'edn b\'e1n nghi, nh\uc0\u432 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u361 ng th\'edch u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ch\'e9n nh\u7887  l\'fac \u259 n t\u7889 i, c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i nh\u7919 ng lo\u7841 i r\u432 \u7907 u l\'e0m t\u7915  g\u7841 o u\u7889 ng \'edt v\'f4 h\u7841 i, n\'ean c\u7853 u \u273 \'e0nh mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng nh\u7853 n l\u7845 y: "V\u7853 y ca c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c u\u7889 ng nhi\u7873 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  r\u7845 t th\'edch Tr\'ec Di\'ean qu\u7843 n h\u7855 n th\u7871  n\'e0y, nghe v\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7853 n, c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, ca ca ch\u7881  u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat. A Di\'ean th\'ec u\u7889 ng nhi\u7873 u ch\'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn ch\uc0\u7857 m ch\u7857 m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi u\u7889 ng, b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 u\u7889 ng hai ba ch\'e9n. B\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7853 u ch\u7881  u\u7889 ng t\u7889 i \u273 a m\u7897 t ch\'e9n v\u7899 i \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, n\'e0o c\'f3 t\u7917 u l\u432 \u7907 ng t\u7889 t \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 , th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ch\'e9n th\u7913  ba v\'e0o b\u7909 ng \u273 \'e3 say, m\u7873 m nh\u361 n n\u7857 m tr\'ean b\'e0n, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u7847 u c\u361 ng n\'e2ng kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7853 t v\u7845 t v\u7843  ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y nam nh\'e2n \u273 ang \u273 oan ch\'ednh ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n m\'ecnh, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 th\u7853 t hay m\u7897 ng, ch\u7889 ng m\'e9p b\'e0n \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, l\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 o ch\u7841 y t\u7899 i, ng\u7891 i l\'ean \u273 \'f9i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i m\u7897 t l\u7901 i m\'e0 \'f4m c\u7893  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi vui v\u7867 : "H\'f4m nay A Di\'ean th\u7871  n\'e0o l\u7841 i ngoan v\u7899 i ca v\u7853 y?" H\u7855 n th\u7915 a bi\u7871 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n d\u7909  Tr\'ec Di\'ean u\u7889 ng nhi\u7873 u m\'e0 c\'f2n nghi\'eam trang t\u7887  v\u7867  qu\'e2n t\u7917  ch\'ednh ph\'e1i, c\u7889  \'fd gi\u7843  b\u7897  c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7921 a s\'e1t v\'e0o, d\'f9ng m\u7863 t c\u7885  c\u7885  ph\u7847 n c\u7893  m\'e1t l\u7841 nh c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, say r\u432 \u7907 u l\'e0m m\u7863 t c\u7853 u h\u7891 ng h\u7891 ng, mang theo sinh kh\'ed v\'e0 nhi\u7879 t kh\'ed say l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i: "A Di\'ean nh\u7899  ca ca." C\u7853 u t\u7915  t\u7915  nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\u7881  non.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'e2u n\'e0y h\'f4m qua em n\'f3i r\uc0\u7891 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng vu\u7889 t ve ph\u7847 n g\'e1y m\u7873 m c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng g\u7907 n s\'f3ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ch\'fat dao \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... Em th\'edch Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca."\cb1 \
\cb3 " C\'e2u n\'e0y h\'f4m qua c\uc0\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  to m\u7855 t, m\u7901  m\u7883 t v\'f4 th\u7889  m\'e0 nh\'ecn nam nh\'e2n, t\u7921 a h\u7891  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 "A Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f2n g\'ec kh\'e1c mu\uc0\u7889 n n\'f3i v\u7899 i ca ca sao? C\'f3 g\'ec c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n c\u7843  th\'edch?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7915 ng ch\'fat t\u7915 ng ch\'fat d\u7851 n d\u7855 t, n\'e9t m\u7863 t d\u7883 u d\'e0ng nhu h\'f2a.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... C\'f3." Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay sang \uc0\u7845 n m\u7897 t n\u7909  h\'f4n m\u7873 m m\u7873 m l\'ean m\u7863 t h\u7855 n, "Ch\'ednh l\'e0, em r\u7845 t r\u7845 t th\'edch Ngh\'eanh Chi..."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i c\'f2n ch\u432 a d\u7913 t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u7845 m \'e1p ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o tr\'ean m\'e1 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \u273 \u7847 u vai b\u7883  \u273 \'e8 n\u7863 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 say \u273 \u7871 n b\u7845 t t\u7881 nh nh\'e2n s\u7921 , d\u7921 a \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean vai h\u7855 n ng\u7911 , trong m\u361 i c\'f2n h\u7915  h\u7915 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i n\'e0y. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, nh\'ecn b\u7897  d\'e1ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7911 , b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y b\u7871  c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, d\'f9ng kh\u259 n \u7845 m lau m\u7891  h\'f4i tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u, thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o r\u7891 i m\u7899 i nh\'e9t ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0o trong ch\u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xem nh\uc0\u432  h\u7855 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u kh\'f4ng tr\u7897 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'e0 c\'f2n m\u7845 t n\u7855 m th\'f3c. Ai ng\u7901  A Di\'ean nh\'e0 h\u7855 n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c vi\u7879 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y, m\u7899 i ba ch\'e9n nh\u7887  \u273 \'e3 say th\'e0nh c\'e1i d\u7841 ng n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\'e8m ngh\u297  l\u7841 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7889  \'fd l\u7915 a g\u7841 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ta say nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'e0 \u273 \'fang hay sai, ch\u7881  r\'fat kinh nghi\u7879 m, ngh\u297  sau n\'e0y ph\u7843 i ch\u7885 n lo\u7841 i r\u432 \u7907 u n\u7891 ng \u273 \u7897  th\u7845 p h\u417 n ch\'fat cho c\u7853 u u\u7889 ng, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  A Di\'ean l\u7841 i say \u273 \u7871 n th\u7889 ng kho\'e1i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7917 a \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7841 i ng\u7911  m\u7845 t, g\u7841 t h\u7855 n sang m\u7897 t b\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7911  s\u7899 m, h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7853 y c\u361 ng s\u7899 m, l\'fac t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang ng\u7911  b\'ean c\u7841 nh \'f4m c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7855 p chung m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c ch\u259 n n\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n r\'f5 h\u417 i l\u7841 nh tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u d\u7883 ch s\'e1t l\u7841 i mu\u7889 n l\'e0m \u7845 m cho h\u7855 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u m\'e0 t\u7881 nh gi\u7845 c, m\u7903  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean d\u7853 y r\u7891 i? Nghe l\u7901 i, \u273 \u7915 ng nh\'fac nh\'edch, ng\u7911  c\'f9ng ca ca th\'eam l\'e1t n\u7919 a." N\'f3i xong th\'f2 tay mu\u7889 n \'f4m c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi lu\'f4n ng\u7911  kh\'f4ng s\'e2u, kh\'f4ng n\u7905  qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y h\u7855 n ng\u7911 , nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng c\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng n\u7919 a, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c duy tr\'ec nguy\'ean tr\u7841 ng n\u7857 m cu\u7897 n c\u7841 nh h\u7855 n, b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'e9o m\u7897 t c\'e1i \'f4m v\'e0o l\'f2ng, sau \u273 \'f3 b\u7845 t tri b\u7845 t gi\'e1c thi\u7871 p \u273 i. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u259 n b\u7843 n kh\'f4ng bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 , ch\u7881  l\'e0 gi\u7843  b\u7897  ch\u432 a t\u7881 nh t\'e1o, quang minh ch\'ednh \u273 \u7841 i n\u7857 m \'f4m c\u7853 u th\'eam ch\u7889 c l\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i l\u7847 n n\u7919 a th\'ec m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 l\'ean cao. Sau khi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean ch\'ednh l\'e0 h\u7887 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, bao tay c\u7911 a ca \u273 \'e2u? Ca \u7903  nh\'e0 m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o th\u7871  n\'e0y c\'f3 l\u7841 nh kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7899  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia b\u7903 i v\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7907  l\u7841 nh, bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n c\'f3 m\u7897 t h\u7879  th\u7889 ng s\u432 \u7903 i \u7845 m, m\u7897 t n\u259 m b\u244 \u769 n m\'f9a \u273 \u7873 u m\u7903 , m\'f9a h\'e8 \'edt khi m\u7903 , nh\u432 ng m\'f9a \u273 \'f4ng th\'ec ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng. Ngo\'e0i ra Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f2n c\'f3 hai chi\u7871 c th\u7843 m l\'f4ng c\'e1o, m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i bao tay, lu\'f4n c\u7845 t \u7903  ch\u7895  v\u7899 i tay l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  l\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang \u7903  ch\u7911  tr\u7841 ch Di\u7879 p gia, t\u7847 ng hai trong c\u259 n nh\'e0 n\'e0y v\u7853 y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 h\u7879  th\u7889 ng s\u432 \u7903 i \u7845 m \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7911  nh\u432  trong bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u v\u7853 t d\u7909 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7919  \u7845 m, qu\u7847 n \'e1o h\u7855 n m\u7863 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c m\u7845 y v\u7899 i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\'f9a n\'e0y ch\u7881  m\u7863 c m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \'e1o s\u417 mi. \u272 \'eam h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac m\u7899 i t\u7899 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\'fa \'fd, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ng\u7851 m ngh\u297  m\u7899 i th\u7845 y kh\'f3 hi\u7875 u, kh\'f4ng l\'fd n\'e0o Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  th\'e0nh gia ch\u7911  Di\u7879 p gia m\'e0 \u273 \'e3i ng\u7897  kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t h\u417 n n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 t\u297 nh d\u432 \u7905 ng \u7903  bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n. Ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 th\u7875  \u259 n b\u7899 t c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, c\'e1ch gi\u7843 i th\'edch duy nh\u7845 t l\'e0 ch\'ednh h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng qu\'fd tr\u7885 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u259 m s\'f3c h\u7855 n chu \u273 \'e1o.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\uc0\u7879 c g\'ec, kh\'f4ng l\u7841 nh." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7841 t n\'f3i, "Th\u7847 y thu\u7889 c n\'f3i th\'e2n th\u7875  ta \u273 \'e3 t\u7889 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u, em th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i ta l\u7841 nh nh\u432 ng k\u7923  th\u7921 c ta kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y l\u7841 nh, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n d\'f9ng m\u7845 y th\u7913  \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y sao \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. C\u259 n nh\'e0 n\'e0y b\u7843 n th\'e2n n\'f3 \u273 \'e3 \'e2m, kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \'e1nh m\u7863 t tr\u7901 i, c\'f2n kh\'f4ng \u7845 m b\u7857 ng b\'ean ngo\'e0i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7849 m b\u7849 m, l\u7841 i ngh\u297  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n, "Thu\u7889 c c\u7911 a Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \u273 \'e2u? M\u7845 y ng\'e0y em \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y th\u7847 y thu\u7889 c \u273 \u7871 n xem b\u7879 nh cho ca?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c kia m\u7897 t ng\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ph\u7843 i u\u7889 ng h\u417 n m\u432 \u7901 i lo\u7841 i thu\u7889 c, thu\u7889 c t\'e2y thu\u7889 c ta \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3, th\u7847 y thu\u7889 c ba ng\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n xem b\u7879 nh cho h\u7855 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n. C\u7853 u c\'f2n t\u7915 ng nghe ng\u432 \u7901 i qu\'e9t d\u7885 n trong bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n n\'f3i v\u7899 i th\u7875  tr\u7841 ng Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 , n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i sinh ra \u7903  Di\u7879 p gia \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u259 m s\'f3c c\u7849 n th\u7853 n nh\u432  th\u7871  th\'ec c\'f3 l\u7869  t\u7915  hai n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n. Khi \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7887  nghe xong nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f3c l\u7899 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi sau khi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n r\u7845 t t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, g\u7885 i Ph\'fac b\'e1 \u273 u\u7893 i m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m \u273 \'f3 \u273 i. D\'f9 Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca n\'f3i hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e \u273 \'e3 t\u7889 t h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\u7887 e m\u7841 nh kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n xem b\u7879 nh kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c, tay h\u7855 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng v\u7851 n l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\'e0y mai th\uc0\u7847 y thu\u7889 c s\u7869  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i, tho\'e1ng d\u7915 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, "Thu\u7889 c u\u7889 ng m\u7845 y lo\u7841 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, h\'f4m qua l\'fac em \u273 \u7871 n H\u7913 a gia v\u7899 i l\'fac ch\u432 a ng\u7911  d\u7853 y ta \u273 \'e3 u\u7889 ng r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y h\'f4m nay th\'ec sao?" B\'e2y gi\u7901  h\u7855 n v\u7851 n \u273 ang m\u7863 c \'e1o ng\u7911  l\u7909 a m\'e0u \u273 en l\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 ng d\u7921 a b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh, r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng m\'ecnh t\u7915  l\'fac t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y v\u7851 n ch\u432 a ra kh\u7887 i \u7893 , \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng \u273 \'e3 u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  \u273 i u\u7889 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u259 n s\'e1ng qu\u7843  nhi\'ean th\u7845 y tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t b\'e1t canh thu\u7889 c, ch\u7881  nghe m\'f9i h\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7883  s\u7869  \u273 \u7855 ng c\u7905  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 \u259 n hai xong ph\u7847 n b\u7919 a s\'e1ng, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\'e1t canh thu\u7889 c v\u7851 n ch\u432 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca sao ch\u432 a u\u7889 ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7841  m\u7855 t li\u7871 c n\'f3, m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng bi\u7875 u t\'ecnh: "\u272 \u7855 ng l\u7855 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u432  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y b\u7897  d\u7841 ng \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\'fac ch\u417 i x\u7845 u \u7903  nh\'e0. Ph\u7843 i n\'f3i \u273 \'fang l\'e0 L\'e3o ngoan \u273 \u7891 ng L\'e3o ngoan \u273 \u7891 ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e0ng gi\'e0 t\'ednh t\'ecnh c\'e0ng nh\u432  con n\'edt, ch\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca n\u259 m nay ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n ba m\u432 \u417 i, v\u7853 y m\'e0 c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u n\'e0y. C\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 tr\u432 \u7899 c kia Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c kh\'f4ng s\u7907  \u273 \u7855 ng, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n Ph\'fac b\'e1 b\u432 ng thu\u7889 c g\'ec t\u7899 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7897 t h\u417 i u\u7889 ng h\u7871 t.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (ngoan \uc0\u273 \u7891 ng: \u273 \u7913 a tr\u7867  c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f3 b\u7843 o)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y c\u7853 u c\'f2n ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean ca t\u7909 ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng h\u7887 i "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca kh\'f4ng s\u7907  \u273 \u7855 ng \u432 ?" . Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 tr\u7843  l\u7901 i c\u7853 u th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
