\cb3 H\uc0\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i, trong \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t tr\u7847 m t\u297 nh m\'e0u \u273 en r\'f5 r\'e0ng tho\'e1ng c\'f3 bi th\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y r\'f5.\cb1 \
