\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn nam nh\'e2n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, c\'f3 ch\'fat b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297 : "Trong nh\'e0 c\'f3 m\u7913 t k\u7865 o kh\'f4ng? \u272 \u7875  em \u273 i l\u7845 y."\cb1 \
