\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7845 y \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t mang \'fd tr\'eau ch\u7885 c c\u7911 a \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  th\u7913  g\'ec, m\u7863 t li\u7873 n \u273 \u7887  l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 qu\u7843  b\'e1o \u273 \u7871 n th\u7853 t nhanh, th\u7921 c ra \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 c\'e1ch Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0m n\u361 ng \u273 \'f2i th\u417 m khi c\'f2n b\'e9, thu\u7903  nh\u7887  c\u7853 u sinh b\u7879 nh ph\'e1t s\u7889 t kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi cho \u259 n m\u7913 t, \u259 n socola c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i l\'e0 Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \'f4m d\u7895  h\'f4n h\'f4n m\u7899 i nghe l\u7901 i u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c, \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd truy\u7873 n d\u7883 ch. Kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i b\'e2y gi\u7901  phong th\u7911 y lu\'e2n chuy\u7875 n, bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i d\u7895  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn h\uc0\u7855 n, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ch\u7881  nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "V\u7853 y ca mau u\u7889 ng \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7847 m b\'e1t s\u7913  l\'ean, m\u7897 t b\'ean u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean m\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 y ti\u7871 u \'fd nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, m\u7897 t m\u7921 c kh\'f4ng d\u7901 i m\u7855 t, t\u7915  n\'e9t m\u7863 t l\u7841 i th\u7845 y d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng h\u7873  th\u7845 y \u273 \u7855 ng. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng h\u7855 n \u273 \u7863 t b\'e1t xu\u7889 ng: "Ta u\u7889 ng xong r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\uc0\u7871 c h\u7855 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i, n\u7917 a nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn v\'e0o m\u7855 t h\u7855 n, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7869  v\u432 \u417 n l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m n\u432 \u7899 c thu\u7889 c c\'f2n v\u432 \u417 ng tr\'ean kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng. Trong l\'fac b\u7845 t ng\u7901  kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng b\u7883  nam nh\'e2n tho\u7855 t c\'e1i \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, h\'f4n l\'ean v\'e0nh tai.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  v\'e0nh tai, m\'f4i m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng d\'e1n t\u7915  c\u7857 m d\u7901 i xu\u7889 ng, \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y ph\'eda xa lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng k\'e8n b\u7847 u v\u7899 i ti\u7871 ng g\'e0o kh\'f3c th\'ea l\u432 \u417 ng, giai \u273 i\u7879 u \u273 au th\u432 \u417 ng o\'e1n th\'e1n, nhi\u7877 u l\'f2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\'e1t run, ch\u7881  h\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  b\u7883 t k\'edn tai, ch\u7863 n \'e2m thanh kia l\u7841 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\uc0\u7853 t m\'ecnh, \u273 \u432 a tay kh\u7869  \u273 \u7849 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ra, ng\u7891 i th\u7859 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, ca nghe, h\'ecnh nh\u432  l\'e0 Tr\u7845 n H\u7891 n Kh\'fac."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y s\u432  m\'f4n c\u7849 n tr\u7885 ng h\u417 n m\u7885 i khi, \u273 \u432 a tang b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\u7845 u Tr\u7845 n H\u7891 n Kh\'fac, ch\u7881  khi c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t oan, thi bi\u7871 n ho\u7863 c h\'f3a th\'e0nh L\u7879  qu\u7927  nguy hi\u7875 m m\u7899 i d\'f9ng Tr\u7845 n H\u7891 n Kh\'fac. Tr\u7845 n H\u7891 n Kh\'fac v\'e0 An H\u7891 n Kh\'fac ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\u7919  kh\'e1c nhau, t\u7915  \u273 \'f3 m\'e0 hi\u7875 u r\u7857 ng l\'e0 \u273 ang tr\u7845 n \'e1p m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i an t\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t l\'e0 nh\'e0 ai l\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n, l\'e0 L\'e2m Tr\u7909  \u7903  H\u7913 a gia kia? Nh\u432 ng H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i L\'e2m Tr\u7909  ngay c\u7843  h\u7891 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng g\u7885 i v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, sao l\u7841 i ph\u7843 i d\'f9ng Tr\u7845 n H\u7891 n Kh\'fac?\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi theo \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i th\u7859 ng l\'ean, s\u7917 a sang l\u7841 i c\u7893  \'e1o, trong m\u7855 t tho\'e1ng hi\u7879 n ch\'fat kh\'f4ng vui, nh\u432 ng r\u7845 t nhanh b\'ecnh ph\u7909 c t\'e2m t\'ecnh, \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n l\'e0 Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca tao nh\'e3: "A Di\'ean t\'f2 m\'f2 th\'ec ch\'fang ta \u273 i xem, n\u417 i n\'e0y qu\u7843  th\u7853 t \u273 \'e3 m\u432 \u7901 i n\u259 m kh\'f4ng nghe th\u7845 y Tr\u7845 n H\u7891 n Kh\'fac r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe Di\uc0\u7879 p gia tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p ch\u7903  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i. C\'e0ng \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n ch\u7895  kia, ti\u7871 ng k\'e8n b\u7847 u l\u7841 i c\'e0ng l\u7899 n, may m\'e0 m\u7897 t l\'e1t sau \u273 \'e3 ng\u7915 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7853 n ra \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 h\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec gia. L\'f2ng c\u7853 u l\u7849 m b\u7849 m m\u7897 t c\'e2u, ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i H\u7913 a gia m\'e0 l\'e0 Tr\'ec gia?\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe d\uc0\u7915 ng l\u7841 i \u7903  ph\'eda xa, qu\u7843 n s\u7921  Di\u7879 p gia nh\u7853 n ra chi\u7871 c xe v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n, c\'e1ch c\u7917 a s\u7893  xe h\u7841  xu\u7889 ng m\u7897 t n\u7917 a b\'e1o v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Tam gia, ng\u432 \u7901 i g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7897 c l\'e3o c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia, \u273 \'eam qua tin qua \u273 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c truy\u7873 n t\u7899 i, ng\'e0i n\'f3i Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u \u273 ang \u7903  \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y n\'ean t\'f4i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m b\u7903 i v\'ec chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y m\'e0 qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u ng\'e0i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0 con th\u7913  ba c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p gia, b\'e2y gi\u7901  tuy r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  th\'e0nh gia ch\u7911  nh\u432 ng l\'e3o nh\'e2n trong nh\'e0 v\u7851 n quen g\u7885 i h\u7855 n Tam gia; Ph\'fac b\'e1 v\u7851 n lu\'f4n h\u7847 u h\u7841  L\'e3o nh\'e2n c\'f2n g\u7885 i h\u7855 n l\'e0 Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "B\'e2y gi\u7901  t\'ecnh h\'ecnh th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia gi\u7843 m th\u7845 p thanh \'e2m: "Tin t\u7913 c n\'f3i v\u7883  t\u7897 c l\'e3o kia trong \u273 \'eam \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u7847 m \u297  \u273 \'f2i g\u7863 p Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  \u273 ang b\u7871  quan, n\'f3i Tr\'ec gia c\'f3 qu\u7927 , sau \u273 \'f3 tin l\u7841 i b\'e1o v\u7883  t\u7897 c l\'e3o \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n, ng\u432 \u7901 i trong Tr\'ec gia n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng, ch\u7881  s\u7907  s\u7869  thi bi\u7871 n, b\'e8n d\'f9ng thu\u7853 t *phong quan tr\u7845 n t\'e0 \u273 \u7875  tr\u7845 n thi th\u7875 . B\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 ang th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n nghi th\u7913 c \u7903  \u273 \u7841 o tr\'e0ng, l\'e0m xong s\u7869  \u273 \u432 a ra m\u7897  t\u7893  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia \u7903  sau n\'fai \u273 \u7875  'Ch\'f4n c\u7845 t'."\cb1 \
