\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec. Qu\u7843 n gia c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t \u273 i\u7873 u lui xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\'f5 r\'e0ng. \u272 ang y\'ean l\'e0nh sao ph\u7843 i s\u7907  thi bi\u7871 n, nh\u432 ng khi c\'f2n b\'e9 \u7903  Tr\'ec gia c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p m\u7897 t v\'e0i th\u7913  kh\'f4ng s\u7841 ch s\u7869 , \u273 \'e2y coi nh\u432  l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n ri\'eang nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta, ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u y\'ean l\u7863 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \uc0\u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ca ca ngh\u7881  \u7903  \u273 \'e2y \u273 i, em qua \u273 \'f3 xem th\u7917 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7913  nh\u7845 t l\'e0 th\'e2n th\u7875  kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 e, th\u7913  hai l\'e0 th\'e2n ph\u7853 n hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng n\'e0y, ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i tr\'ean xe s\u7869  t\u7889 t h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi o\'e1n tr\'e1ch li\u7871 c c\u7853 u: "C\'e1i g\'ec n\'e1o nhi\u7879 t c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n h\'f3ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i ta tr\u7845 n t\'e0 ch\'f4n ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t em c\u361 ng \u273 \'f2i xem, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng s\u7907  \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i t\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, l\u7841 i g\u7847 n \'f4m m\u7863 t h\u7855 n h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, c\'e1i g\'ec em c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng s\u7907 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o \u273 \u7889 i ph\'f3 c\u7853 u, nghi\'eang m\u7863 t, ph\u7845 t ph\u7845 t tay b\u7843 o c\u7853 u xu\u7889 ng xe, kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng l\u7841 i r\'f5 r\'e0ng cong l\'ean \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\'f9y ti\u7879 n h\'f3ng chuy\u7879 n m\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e2u "Tr\'ec gia c\'f3 qu\u7927 " c\u7911 a qu\u7843 n s\u7921  Di\u7879 p gia kh\u417 i l\'ean h\u7913 ng th\'fa c\u7911 a c\u7853 u. C\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\u7899  m\'ecnh v\'ec sao m\'e0 tr\u7903  v\u7873 , c\u361 ng nh\u7899  r\'f5 Tr\'ec gia, nh\u7845 t l\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'e3 m\u432 u t\'ednh l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng chuy\u7879 n \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia \u273 \u7875  h\u7841 i m\'ecnh nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o. C\u7853 u l\u7901  m\u7901  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\'f3 quan h\u7879  v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n h\u7841 i c\u7853 u kia, ho\u7863 c c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7881  l\'e0 c\u7853 u ngh\u297  nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u len qua \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i t\u7899 i ch\u7895  tr\u7889 ng ch\'ednh gi\u7919 a nh\'ecn, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y tr\'ean s\'e0n \u273 \'e1 xanh \u7903  \u273 \u7841 o tr\'e0ng v\u7869  m\u7897 t ph\'e1p tr\u7853 n tr\u7845 n t\'e0 m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  t\u432 \u417 i, gi\u7919 a tr\u7853 n \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c quan t\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en nh\'ecn c\'f3 v\u7867  r\u7845 t n\u7863 ng, b\u7889 n v\'e1ch quan t\'e0i c\u361 ng d\'f9ng chu sa v\u7869  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i ph\'e1p tr\u7853 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c quan t\'e0i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  n\u7893 i l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y khi n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghi th\uc0\u7913 c \u273 \'e3 ti\u7871 n h\'e0nh \u273 \u7871 n b\u432 \u7899 c cu\u7889 i, ch\'edn ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia ti\u7871 n t\u7899 i khi\'eang quan t\'e0i l\'ean, ti\u7871 ng k\'e8n b\u7847 u vang l\'ean, m\u7897 t \u273 o\'e0n ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i c\'f9ng quan t\'e0i \u273 i v\u7873  h\u432 \u7899 ng m\u7897  t\u7893  Tr\'ec gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng ngay h\u432 \u7899 ng nh\'f3m ng\u432 \u7901 i khi\'eang quan t\'e0i ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n, th\u7845 y v\u7853 y c\u7853 u lui v\u7873  sau m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c theo ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  l\u7841 i tho\'e1ng c\'e1i bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7845 t. \u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y nh\'f3m ng\u432 \u7901 i khi\'eang quan t\'e0i \u273 i qua, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda quan t\'e0i v\u7869  \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7857 ng tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p tr\u7845 n t\'e0 kia \'97\'97 trong \u273 \'f3 h\'ecnh nh\u432  truy\u7873 n ra ti\u7871 ng khua \u273 \u7853 p r\u7845 t nh\u7887 , d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean trong \u273 ang \u273 ang kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng \u273 \u7853 p quan t\'e0i...\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7897 i k\'e8n b\u7847 u \u273 i qua, r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 che l\u7845 p ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 kia, Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7847 n xa, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng m\'ecnh v\u7915 a nghe th\u7845 y ph\u7843 i ch\u259 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7902  \u273 \'e2y \u273 a s\u7889  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec gia, ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n c\'f3 kh\'f4ng \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7853 n ra c\u7853 u, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n sinh th\'eam chuy\u7879 n, nh\'ecn \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i khi\'eang quan t\'e0i \u273 i xa r\u7891 i ch\u7841 y v\u7873  xe Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\'ecnh th\u7843 n nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "\u272 \'e3 h\'e0i l\'f2ng r\u7891 i? Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n qua xem n\u7919 a ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7847 u chuy\u7875 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i, l\u7841 i \'f4m l\u7845 y c\'e1nh tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\u7899 i g\u7847 n h\u7855 n n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7899 m n\u7919 a, c\'f9ng Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca v\u7873  nh\'e0."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn c\u7853 u l\'e2u h\u417 n, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a tay ni\u7871 t g\'e1y c\u7853 u v\'e0i c\'e1i, n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i: "Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i, l\u7841 i c\u7889  \'fd d\u7909  ca ca." N\'f3i xong l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7843 o t\'e0i x\u7871  l\'e1i xe quay v\u7873  Di\u7879 p gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, trong n\uc0\u7897 i t\'e2m l\u7841 i nh\u432  c\u7887  d\u7841 i lan tr\'e0n. Thu\u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c hai ng\u432 \u7901 i qu\'e1 g\u7847 n g\u361 i, c\u7853 u l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng ch\'fat nh\u7853 n ra l\u7847 n n\'e0y sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  n\'ean vi di\u7879 u th\u7871  n\'e0o. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'e0 c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u, c\u361 ng th\'e2n m\u7853 t v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, \'f4m c\u7853 u, h\'f4n c\u7853 u, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 qu\'fd m\u7871 n v\'e0 th\'e2n thi\u7871 t \u273 \u417 n thu\u7847 n, h\'f4n l\'ean m\'e1 v\'e0 tr\'e1n, nh\u7865  nh\u432  gi\'f3 tho\u7843 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng t\u7915  ng\'e0y c\u7853 u theo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7903  l\u7841 i Di\u7879 p gia, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  n\u7909  h\'f4n c\'f3 ch\'fat li\u7873 u l\u297 nh kia, h\u7871 t th\u7843 y \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7893 i \u273 i\u7879 u, c\u361 ng \u273 \u7893 i \'fd ngh\u297 a \'97\'97 l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tuy\u7879 t s\u7869  kh\'f4ng h\'f4n m\'f4i c\u7853 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y, n\u7909  h\'f4n bao h\'e0m d\u7909 c ni\u7879 m v\'e0 chi\u7871 m h\u7919 u, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t sinh gi\u7919 a t\'ecnh nh\'e2n. Nh\u7919 ng thay \u273 \u7893 i n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7897 c l\u7897  ra t\u7915  nh\u7919 ng n\u7909  h\'f4n, nh\u7919 ng c\'e1i \'f4m, ch\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng ai v\u7841 ch tr\u7847 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ai ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng ti\u7871 n th\'eam m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c. C\u7843  hai ng\u7847 m hi\u7875 u m\'e0 m\u7863 c bi\u7871 n h\'f3a thu\u7853 n theo t\u7921  nhi\'ean, ngo\'e0i m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng g\u7907 n s\'f3ng, d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng l\u7841 i l\'e0 s\'f3ng t\'ecnh m\'e3nh li\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau b\uc0\u7919 a tr\u432 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i gi\u7889 ng bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng "Gi\'e1m s\'e1t" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c, t\'e2m s\u7921  v\u7899 i h\u7855 n cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng nh\u7919 ng n\u259 m qua \u7903  b\'ean ngo\'e0i, th\u7901 i gian tr\'f4i qua r\u7845 t nhanh, nh\'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 t\u7899 i bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7911  c\'f9ng nhau nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 ch\'ecm v\'e0o gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng, trong m\u7897 ng c\u7853 u m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng th\u7845 y b\u7843 n th\'e2n b\u7883  giam trong m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c quan t\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en, b\u7883  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 tr\'f3i bu\u7897 c, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7845 t \u273 au, ra s\u7913 c \u273 \u7853 p quan t\'e0i mu\u7889 n tho\'e1t ra. C\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ti\u7871 ng t\u7909 ng ch\'fa v\u259 n, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\u7863 t ch\u7911  nh\'e2n nh\u7919 ng thanh \'e2m kia, nh\u432 ng trong \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t hi\u7879 n ra t\u7915 ng g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t bi\u7871 n d\u7841 ng v\u7863 n v\u7865 o d\u7919  t\u7907 n, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7853 u. Kh\'ed l\u7921 c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u y\u7871 u d\u7847 n, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n c\u7853 u tho\'e1t ra ngo\'e0i, t\u7845 t c\u7843  b\u7841 n b\'e8 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u mu\u7889 n phong \u7845 n c\u7853 u, khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u ch\u7871 t trong ng\u7897 t ng\u7841 t t\u259 m t\u7889 i, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  si\'eau sinh.\cb1 \
