\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7845 u ch\'fat t\'e2m t\u432  n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u nghi\u7871 n r\u259 ng nghi\u7871 n l\u7907 i m\'e0 ngh\u297  ti\u7875 u h\u7895 n \u273 \u7843 n nh\'e0 m\'ecnh th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng c\'e2u ng\u432 \u7901 i, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c ngay ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7883  c\'e2u \u273 \u7871 n s\u7889 ng l\u7841 i, r\u7891 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 c\'e0ng th\'eam lu\'e2n h\'e3m, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mu\u7889 n \u7913 c hi\u7871 p c\u7853 u, ch\u7901  \u7913 c hi\u7871 p no r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'e0ng c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u h\u417 n. Ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng th\u7883 t trong l\'f2ng, mu\u7889 n h\u7855 n s\u7889 ng mu\u7889 n h\u7855 n ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  trong ti\u7875 u l\'e2u g\u7847 n nh\u432  ng\u259 n c\'e1ch v\u7899 i th\u7871  gian m\'e0 qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y nhau m\u7845 y ng\'e0y, l\u7877  t\u7871  thi\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghi th\uc0\u7913 c t\u7871  t\u7921  di\u7877 n ra ba ng\'e0y li\'ean t\u7909 c, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i h\u7855 n ch\u7881  tham d\u7921  bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng ng\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean. V\u7873  \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'e1i l\u7841 i r\u7845 t t\'e1n th\'e0nh, c\u7853 u lu\'f4n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i h\u7843 o h\u7843 o t\u297 nh d\u432 \u7905 ng, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  lu\'f4n chi\u7873 u \'fd b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\'e0m x\u7857 ng l\'e0m b\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u417  th\u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n y\u7871 u, b\'e0n tay l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i xu\u7889 ng xe, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7905  c\'e1nh tay h\u7855 n c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i v\'e0o. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7855 m tay c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec. \cb1 \
\cb3 Trong s\uc0\u7843 nh m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n \u273 \u7911 , hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a \u273 i v\'e0o li\u7873 n c\'f3 v\'f4 s\u7889  \'e1nh m\u7855 t r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7905  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i v\'e0o v\u7883  tr\'ed c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, b\u7843 n th\'e2n ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh. Ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i trong l\u7877  t\u7871  thi\'ean ph\'e2n d\u7921 a theo c\'e1c nh\'e0 c\'e1c ph\'e1i, n\u417 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 ang ng\u7891 i l\'e0 c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p gia, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng th\'ec nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin nh\u7855 n c\u7911 a H\u7913 a H\'e2n: "Ph\u7853 n b\u7883  \u273 \'e0o g\'f3c t\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a t\'f4i s\u7855 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 ng th\u7921 c r\u7891 i, Di\u7879 p phu nh\'e2n, c\u7853 u c\'f3 c\'f2n nh\u7899  hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u l\'e0 b\u7841 n trai t\'f4i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i m\u7897 t tin "\u272 \u7915 ng nh\'e1o". M\u7845 y ng\'e0y qua Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi lu\'f4n n\'f3i c\u7853 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y "A Di\'ean \u273 \u7915 ng nh\'e1o", ho\u7863 c l\'e0 "Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i", Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7885 c theo, v\'f4 th\u7913 c m\'e0 d\'f9ng, kh\'f4ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  th\'e2n m\u7853 t trong hai ch\u7919  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i qua c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn di \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i: "\u272 \u7915 ng nh\'e1o '? C\u7843  hai quan h\u7879  v\u7851 n r\u7845 t t\u7889 t nh\u7881 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n ch\uc0\u432 a k\u7883 p l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin nh\u7855 n c\u7911 a H\u7913 a H\'e2n, kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "Di\u7879 p phu nh\'e2n? C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 ." L\'fac n\'e0y n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 th\u7853 t h\u417 n h\u7859 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7913 c kh\u7855 c kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng k\'eau m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca......"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i li\u7871 c c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "\u7914 ? C\'f2n g\u7885 i ca ca? Nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c n\'ean l\'e0m hay kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\'e0m \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m. \u272 \'eam qua g\u7885 i th\u7871  n\'e0o? G\u7885 i l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n xem n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\uc0\u7907 n m\u7855 t tr\u7915 ng h\u7855 n, ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7915  m\u7863 t xu\u7889 ng ch\'e2n \u273 \u7873 u n\'f3ng l\'ean, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng b\u7887  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u "Em \u273 i v\u7879  sinh" xong ch\u7841 y tr\u7889 i ch\u7871 t \'97\'97 c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i \u273 i r\u7917 a m\u7863 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia nh\'ecn b\u7897  d\'e1ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u432 \u7899 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i m\'e0 c\'f2n ch\u7841 y, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n khom ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7887 i: "Tam gia, Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec ch\u7913 ? C\'f3 c\u7847 n cho ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i xem kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kho\'e1t tay \'e1o c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, trong \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t s\'e2u hi\u7879 n l\'ean \'e1nh s\'e1ng nhu h\'f2a: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec. A Di\'ean l\'e0 *bi\u7879 t n\u7919 u th\'f4i, l\'e1t n\u7919 a s\u7869  quay l\u7841 i."\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (*bi\uc0\u7879 t n\u7919 u: n\'f3i m\u7897 t \u273 \u7857 ng l\'e0m m\u7897 t n\u7867 o)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng v\uc0\u7879  sinh \u7903  sau \u273 \u7841 i s\u7843 nh, \u273 i qua m\u7897 t hoa vi\'ean nh\u7887 , l\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7915  ph\'f2ng v\u7879  sinh \u273 i ra th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i quen thu\u7897 c \u273 \u7913 ng c\u7841 nh b\u7891 n hoa, b\'ean c\u7841 nh kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai kh\'e1c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 , m\'e0 con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kia l\u7841 i l\'e0 con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng duy nh\u7845 t, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 oan gia ng\'f5 h\u7865 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7855 t nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng \u273 i qua, l\'fac \u273 i ngang qua Tr\'ec Dung ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng g\u7885 i c\u7853 u l\u7841 i: "Tr\'ec Di\'ean."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n, quay ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng l\'ean ti\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "N\uc0\u7871 u \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  \u273 u\u7893 i \u273 i sao c\'f2n mu\u7889 n tr\u7903  v\u7873 , anh ngh\u297  r\u7857 ng b\'e1n th\'e2n cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'ec h\u7855 n s\u7869  ch\u7889 ng l\u432 ng cho anh sao? C\'f3 th\u7875  gi\'fap anh quay v\u7873  l\'e0m ch\'e1u \u273 \'edch t\'f4n th\u7915 a k\u7871  Tr\'ec Gia sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng xu\'f4i tai nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7887  qua n\u7917 a c\'e2u sau ch\'f3i tai c\u7911 a g\'e3, n\'e2ng m\u7855 t nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng Tr\'ec Dung: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n b\u7913 c ch\u7871 t t\'f4i \'e0, c\u7853 u ngh\u297  t\'f4i s\u7869  tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Anh n\'f3i t\'f4i h\uc0\u7841 i anh?" Tr\'ec Dung c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7841 o m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, "Ch\'f3 nh\'e0 c\'f3 tang, anh cho r\u7857 ng t\'f4i c\'f2n \u273 \u7875  \'fd anh s\u7889 ng ch\u7871 t ra sao \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\

\f2\i \cb3 (*ch\'f3 nh\'e0 c\'f3 tang: \'fd n\'f3i ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 n\u417 i n\u432 \u417 ng th\'e2n, Tr\'ec Dung \u273 ang n\'f3i Tr\'ec Di\'ean)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n lu\'f4n nh\'ecn v\'e0o m\u7855 t g\'e3. \'c1nh m\u7855 t g\'e3 kh\u7869  \u273 \u7843 o sang ph\u7843 i. G\'e3 \u273 ang n\'f3i d\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a d\'e1m ch\u7855 c s\u7921  ki\u7879 n x\u7843 y ra kia l\'e0 do Tr\'ec Dung l\'e0m th\'ec hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh vi\u7879 c n\'e0y kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i can h\u7879  v\u7899 i g\'e3. B\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'f3i d\u7889 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Dung, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1 quen.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi c\'f2n nh\uc0\u7887  c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u Tr\'ec Dung v\'e0 m\u7865  h\u7855 n r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f3 quan h\u7879  g\'ec v\u7899 i cha m\'ecnh, m\u7865  c\u7853 u s\u7907  c\u7853 u b\u7883  t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng, thu\u7903  nh\u7887  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch r\'f5 r\'e0ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y. B\u7903 i v\'ec tu\u7893 i x\u7845 p x\u7881  n\'ean th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng Tr\'ec Dung t\'ecm g\'e3 ch\u417 i, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7841 n b\'e8 c\u7853 u c\'f2n r\u7845 t vui v\u7867  m\'e0 \u273 i ch\u417 i v\u7899 i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng. Nh\u432 ng th\'f4ng qua quan s\'e1t tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c, c\u7853 u l\u7901  m\u7901  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7865  c\u7853 u r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng th\'edch Tr\'ec Dung v\'e0 m\u7865  g\'e3, m\'e0 so v\u7899 i m\'ecnh, ph\u7909  th\'e2n l\u7841 i thi\'ean v\u7883  Tr\'ec Dung h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec sao r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\'ecnh m\u7855 c l\u7895 i, k\u7867  n\'f3i d\u7889 i l\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung nh\u432 ng cha lu\'f4n tr\'e1ch ph\u7841 t m\'ecnh, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec sao cha lu\'f4n b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'f3i d\u7889 i v\u7909 ng v\u7873  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Dung che m\u7855 t. Sau n\'e0y l\u7899 n l\'ean m\u7899 i hi\u7875 u, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c ai th\u7853 t ai gi\u7843 , m\'e0 b\u7903 i trong th\'e2m t\'e2m v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 thi\'ean v\u7883  g\'e3. Nh\u432 ng trong qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh "Nh\u7853 n r\'f5 b\u7897  m\u7863 t th\u7853 t c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Dung" n\'e0y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn th\u7845 u b\u7897  d\u7841 ng khi n\'f3i d\u7889 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Dung, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng m\u7897 t c\'e2u, c\u7853 u s\u7869  bi\u7871 t g\'e3 \u273 ang n\'f3i th\u7853 t hay gi\u7843 , c\'f3 l\u7915 a ng\u432 \u7901 i hay kh\'f4ng, \u273 \'e3 nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, Tr\'ec Dung \u7903  ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ch\'fat ti\u7871 n b\u7897 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng mu\uc0\u7889 n l\'e3ng ph\'ed th\'eam th\u7901 i gian tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Dung, b\u7887  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u "L\'e0m hay kh\'f4ng l\'e0m t\u7921  c\u7853 u r\'f5, v\'ec sao t\'f4i tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n", sau \u273 \'f3 quay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i. Tr\'ec Dung l\u7841 i ti\u7871 n l\'ean m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c ng\u259 n c\u7853 u: "Tr\'ec Di\'ean, t\'f4i khuy\'ean anh m\u7897 t c\'e2u, mau r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n g\'e3, im l\u7863 ng g\u7841 t tay g\'e3 ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i. C\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ti\u7871 p x\'fac tay Tr\'ec Dung c\u7853 u h\u417 i nh\'edu m\'e0y, tay Tr\'ec Dung cho c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \'e2m h\'e0n \u432 \u7899 t l\u7841 nh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  tay thi th\u7875  b\'f2 ra t\u7915  trong \u273 \u7897 ng, t\'f3m l\u7845 y ch\'e2n ng\u432 \u7901 i, k\'e9o ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n \u7903  l\u7841 i t\u7917  \u273 \u7883 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi quay l\uc0\u7841 i ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i tinh th\u7847 n tr\u7903  n\'ean m\u7845 t t\u7853 p trung, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn ra c\u7853 u th\u7845 t th\u7847 n, kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c tr\'eau c\u7853 u n\u7919 a, \u273 \u7907 i th\'eam m\u7897 t l\'e1t r\u7891 i l\u7845 y c\u7899  kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 e mang theo Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a ng\u7891 i l\'ean xe Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7887 i th\u7859 ng: "Em v\u7915 a g\u7863 p ai? V\u7915 a tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 \'e3 thay \u273 \u7893 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\'ec Dung." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7845 u gi\u7871 m, "Em c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7853 u ta \u273 ang t\'ecm c\u417  h\u7897 i h\u7841 i em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ngh\u297  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n, quay sang Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i: "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, ca ca c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7841 y em m\u7897 t v\'e0i bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p b\u7843 o v\u7879  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng kh\'f4ng? N\u7871 u Tr\'ec Dung th\u7853 t s\u7921  b\u7883  d\u7891 n \'e9p, b\u7845 t ch\u7845 p m\'e0 h\u7841 i em th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7889 ng c\u7857 m th\u7843 n nhi\'ean nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "H\u7855 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7915 a k\u7871  Tr\'ec Gia, em b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 Di\u7879 p phu nh\'e2n, h\u7855 n h\u7841 i em l\'e0m g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ch\'fat b\uc0\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297 , th\u7903  d\'e0i g\u7885 i h\u7855 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  kh\'f4ng nh\'fac nh\'edch, b\u7897  d\'e1ng kh\'f4ng m\'e0ng th\u7871  s\u7921 : "Nh\u432 ng c\'e1ch b\u7843 o m\u7879 nh th\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7841 y em."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Hi\uc0\u7879 n t\u7841 i nghe em g\u7885 i Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, ta kh\'f4ng v\u7915 a l\'f2ng n\u7919 a, g\u7885 i c\'e1i kh\'e1c, ca ca s\u7869  d\u7841 y em."\cb1 \
