\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "... Bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7885 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \'e9p c\u7853 u: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean cho em n\u7907 , bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i nh\u7899  ph\u7843 i tr\u7843  c\u7843  l\'e3i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi tr\uc0\u7903  l\u7841 i Di\u7879 p gia, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng d\u7851 n c\u7853 u v\u7873  ti\u7875 u l\'e2u ngay m\'e0 b\u7843 o t\'e0i x\u7871  l\'e1i \u273 \u7871 n t\'e0ng th\u432  l\'e2u ph\'eda t\'e2y ch\u7911  tr\u7841 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\uc0\u7871 t r\'f5 nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i n\'e0y ch\u7881  truy\u7873 n th\u7915 a trong gia t\u7897 c, ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e9p v\'e0o, kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i d\u7851 n c\u7853 u th\u7859 ng t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y ch\u7885 n s\'e1ch, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  c\u7917 a nh\'ecn v\'e0o trong, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ti\u7871 n v\'e0o, do d\u7921  nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, em \u273 i v\'e0o th\'ec kh\'f4ng hay l\u7855 m. N\u417 i \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i v\'e0o \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m: "Ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p theo h\u7885  Di\u7879 p c\u7911 a ta, m\u7897 t c\'e1i t\'e0ng th\u432  l\'e2u c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f4ng th\u7875  v\'e0o." N\'f3i xong tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p d\u7851 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'e0ng th\uc0\u432  l\'e2u c\'f3 t\u7845 t c\u7843  ba t\u7847 ng, b\'ean trong kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai, t\u7915 ng d\'e3y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 gi\'e1 s\'e1ch b\u7857 ng g\u7895  m\'e0u \u273 en cao th\u7859 ng l\'ean tr\u7847 n nh\'e0, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i v\'e0o r\u7891 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  \u273 \'e2u. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi gi\'fap c\u7853 u ch\u7885 n v\'e0i quy\u7875 n \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n d\u7877  \u7913 ng d\u7909 ng, \u273 \u7871 n khi v\u7873  ti\u7875 u l\'e2u l\u7841 i l\u7845 y s\u7893  ghi ch\'e9p h\u7891 i nh\u7887  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u432 a cho c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u tham kh\u7843 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u trong th\u7901 i gian ng\u7855 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o t\u297 nh t\'e2m h\u7885 c, sau khi quay l\u7841 i ti\u7875 u l\'e2u tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u ch\u259 m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c, u\u7889 ng xong li\u7873 n b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 . M\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng b\u7883  \'f4m l\'ean l\u7847 u c\u7853 u s\u7907  h\u7871 t h\u7891 n, ch\u7881  s\u7907  th\u7875  l\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  n\u7893 i s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn m\u7855 t c\u7853 u m\u7903  l\u7899 n, c\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4n tr\'e1n c\u7853 u: "Em s\u7907  c\'e1i g\'ec? Ca ca c\u361 ng \u273 \'e2u c\'f3 \u259 n th\u7883 t em."\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7907  c\u417  th\u7875  anh kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. L\u7901 i n\'e0y d\u7841 o trong mi\u7879 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t v\'f2ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nu\u7889 t tr\u7903  v\'e0o. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t kh\'f4n, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng n\'f3i nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i ch\u7885 c t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'e0y n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7919 a t\u7889 i \u259 n \u7903  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 . Bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u259 n qua l\u259 n l\u7841 i hai l\u7847 n xong m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng m\'e0 ng\u7911 , th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n b\u7843 y gi\u7901  t\u7889 i m\u7899 i t\u7881 nh, c\u417 m t\u7889 i \u273 \'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  xong, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7853 m r\'e3i \u259 n, h\u417 n t\'e1m gi\u7901  \u259 n xong th\'ec qu\u7843 n gia t\u7899 i, n\'f3i l\'e0 c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n mu\u7889 n b\'e1o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\'f3 vi\u7879 c kh\u7849 n c\u7845 p nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\u7847 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi x\u7917  l\'fd th\'ec qu\u7843 n gia s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\'f9y ti\u7879 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7875 u l\'e2u qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y h\u7855 n. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f9ng qu\u7843 n gia qua th\u432  ph\'f2ng, ch\u432 a \u273 \u432 \u417 \u803 c v\'e0i ph\'fat \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , qu\u7843 n gia \u273 i theo sau h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 a c\u7857 m v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, n\'f3i v\u7899 i qu\u7843 n gia: "T\u7921  \'f4ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u \u273 i, \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, \u273 \u7875  A Di\'ean t\u7921  quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng \uc0\u273 o\'e1n chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y li\'ean quan t\u7899 i m\'ecnh nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia h\u7841  m\u7855 t, r\u7845 t cung k\'ednh m\'e0 l\u7863 p l\u7841 i tin t\u7913 c v\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c: "Khuya h\'f4m nay sau khi k\u7871 t th\'fac b\u7919 a t\u7889 i sau l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i, Tr\'ec ti\'ean sinh \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean t\'e9 x\u7881 u, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a v\u7873  Tr\'ec gia, b\'ean \u273 \'f3 mu\u7889 n Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u quay v\u7873  g\u7863 p Tr\'ec ti\'ean sinh."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'edu m\'e0y: "V\uc0\u7853 y l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec ti\'ean sinh trong l\uc0\u7901 i qu\u7843 n gia n\'f3i ch\'ednh l\'e0 cha c\u7853 u Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, t\u7893  ph\u7909  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u hi\u7879 n \u273 ang b\u7871  quan, l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i l\u7847 n n\'e0y l\'e0 do cha c\u7853 u \u273 \u7841 i di\u7879 n Tr\'ec gia tham gia. Nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n \u273 ang kh\u7887 e m\u7841 nh \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean v\'f4 c\u7899  t\'e9 x\u7881 u, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i g\u7885 i c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873 , c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng nghi ng\u7901  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i Tr\'ec gia l\u7841 i c\'f3 \'e2m m\u432 u c\u7841 m b\u7851 y g\'ec hay kh\'f4ng, tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7843 n th\'e2n ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng \u273 \u7875  t\'ednh k\u7871 , ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  Tr\'ec Dung th\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'fd do g\'ec mu\u7889 n \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u v\'e0o ch\u7895  ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia kh\'e9o l\'e9o \u273 \'e1p: "B\'ean kia n\'f3i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t l\u7855 m, Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7863 p m\u7897 t l\u7847 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ph\u7849 y tay: "\'d4ng n\'f3i th\u7859 ng \u273 i, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c ra sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia c\'e2n nh\u7855 c ch\u7899 p m\u7855 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... C\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 l\u7847 n g\u7863 p cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7891 ng t\u7917  Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i co l\u7841 i. Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n n\u259 m nay ch\u7881  m\u7899 i qua n\u259 m m\u432 \u417 i, bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng \u7903  nghi th\u7913 c t\u7871  t\u7921  c\u7853 u c\'f2n th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n t\u7915  xa, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\u7845 u hi\u7879 u s\u7869  l\'e0 l\u7847 n g\u7863 p cu\u7889 i. Nh\u432 ng qu\u7843 n gia kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i d\u7889 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, Di\u7879 p gia Tr\'ec gia r\u7845 t nghi\'eam, qu\u7843 n gia c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i h\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'f4 d\u7909 ng, \'f4ng n\'f3i v\u7853 y th\'ec h\u7859 n l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i x\'e1c minh tin t\u7913 c m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7881  nghe t\u7915  m\u7897 t ph\'eda Tr\'ec gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn v\uc0\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng: "Em mu\u7889 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\'ecn th\u7917 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 a ra b\u7845 t k\u7923  b\'ecnh lu\u7853 n n\'e0o, nghe v\u7853 y ch\u7881  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Ta v\'e0 em c\'f9ng \u273 i." Sau \u273 \'f3 nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda qu\u7843 n gia: "Chu\u7849 n b\u7883  xe."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn s\uc0\u7855 c tr\u7901 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i: "Kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 \'e2u, bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u ca ch\u432 a ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i, t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'e0 n\'ean ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i. Em... \u273 i xem m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i s\u7869  v\u7873 , d\'f9 sao Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m \u273 o\u7841 n tuy\u7879 t quan h\u7879  cha con v\u7899 i em, "\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \'fd ki\u7871 n g\'ec m\'e0 c\'f9ng c\u7853 u l\'ean xe: "Em v\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 o\u7841 n tuy\u7879 t quan h\u7879 , v\u7853 y ta kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  tang n\u7919 a, nh\u432 ng chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y ta sao c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\'f4ng \u273 i c\'f9ng em. Ta ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i trong xe c\u361 ng th\u7871 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe ch\uc0\u7841 y m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\'e1ch Tr\'ec gia ng\'e0y c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c xung quanh c\u361 ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng quen. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7899  l\u7841 i khi m\'ecnh c\'f2n nh\u7887 , trong tr\'ed nh\u7899  m\u417  h\u7891 , khi c\u7853 u ba b\u7889 n tu\u7893 i Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n \u273 \u7889 i x\u7917  v\u7899 i c\u7853 u h\'ecnh nh\u432  v\u7851 n r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, c\'f2n mua \u273 \u7891  ch\u417 i cho c\u7853 u, trong \u273 \'f3 th\u7913  c\u7853 u th\'edch nh\u7845 t l\'e0 chi\u7871 c t\'e0u h\u7887 a ch\u7841 y b\u7857 ng \u273 i\u7879 n m\u7899 i nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i b\u7845 y gi\u7901 , Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n mang c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i trong s\'e2n l\u7855 p \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ray nh\u7921 a, ki\'ean nh\u7851 n ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh nh\'ecn c\u7853 u t\'f2 m\'f2 ch\u259 m ch\'fa ng\u7855 m t\'e0u h\u7887 a ch\u7841 y tr\'ean tr\'ean ray.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng th\u7901 i gian \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1 l\'e2u, c\u7853 u d\u7847 n l\u7899 n l\'ean, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n ho\'e0i nghi \u273 o\'e0n t\'e0u m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  v\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ray m\'e0u v\'e0ng kia c\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c do b\u7843 n th\'e2n t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng ra hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7865  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng n\'f3i r\'f5 cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t m\u7899  b\'f2ng bong n\'e0y gi\u7919 a b\'e0 v\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n v\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  ghi nh\u7899 , nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7901 i k\u7875  t\u7915  mi\u7879 ng nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c m\u7899 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n ch\u7855 p v\'e1 ra chuy\u7879 n n\u259 m \u273 \'f3. Trong l\u7901 i nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 , n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n l\'e0 m\u7897 t thanh ni\'ean tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i nh\u432  H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, ch\'e1n gh\'e9t Tr\'ec gia c\u7893  h\u7911  t\u7867  nh\u7841 t, nh\u7901  \u273 \u7845 u tranh th\u7855 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'e0 m\'e0 gi\'e0nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u417  h\u7897 i r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia \u273 i h\u7885 c, c\u361 ng l\'e0 l\'fac \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c quen bi\u7871 t m\u7865  c\u7853 u, c\u361 ng nhanh ch\'f3ng y\'eau nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng \'f4ng l\'e0 con trai tr\u432 \u7903 ng Tr\'ec gia, sau n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ph\u7843 i k\u7871  th\u7915 a Tr\'ec gia, sau khi t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p gia t\u7897 c b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7841 o \'e1p l\u7921 c b\u7913 c b\'e1ch \'f4ng v\u7873  nh\'e0. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng song ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7873 u l\'f9i m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd quay v\u7873  Tr\'ec gia, Tr\'ec gia \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd cho \'f4ng l\u226 \u769 y m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'e2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng; m\'e0 m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac \u7845 y c\'f2n r\u7845 t tr\u7867 , sau khi nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'e2n th\u7871  ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u273 \'e3 v\'ec Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n m\'e0 d\u7913 t kho\'e1t quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh b\u7887  l\u7841 i t\u7845 t c\u7843 , g\u7843  v\'e0o Tr\'ec gia, d\'f9 nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 ngh\u297 a l\'e0 b\'e0 hi sinh s\u7921  nghi\u7879 p, ti\u7873 n \u273 \u7891  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, th\u7853 m ch\'ed r\u7845 t \'edt c\'f3 c\u417  h\u7897 i c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7903  v\u7873  th\u259 m cha m\u7865 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\'fac m\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7873 u t\u7889 t, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n c\u361 ng g\u7855 ng h\u7871 t s\u7913 c che ch\u7903  v\u7907  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, cho d\'f9 \u7903  trong thi\'ean s\u432  th\u7871  gia kh\'f4ng h\u7873  t\u7847 m th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432 ng hai ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n h\u7841 nh ph\'fac ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o. Th\u7871  nh\u432 ng ti\u7879 c vui ch\'f3ng t\'e0n, ngay t\u7841 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7855 p sinh ra, m\u7865  c\u7853 u ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n cha Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c b\'ean ngo\'e0i, h\u417 n n\u7919 a ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 mang thai, ch\u7881  nh\u7887  h\u417 n h\'e0i t\u7917  b\'e0 s\u7855 p sinh b\u7889 n th\'e1ng. S\u7903  d\u297  b\'e0 bi\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y l\'e0 v\'ec Tr\'ec gia kh\'f4ng cho ph\'e9p huy\u7871 t m\u7841 ch Tr\'ec gia l\u432 u l\u7841 c b\'ean ngo\'e0i, cho n\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'f3n ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  \u273 \'f3 v\u7873 , thu x\u7871 p cho \u7903  m\u7897 t c\u259 n nh\'e0 nh\u7887  ngo\'e0i ch\u7911  tr\u7841 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Vi\uc0\u7877 n S\u417 n kh\'f3c l\'f3c ch\u7843 y n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t kh\u7849 n c\u7847 u tha th\u7913 , n\'f3i khi \u273 \'f3 \'f4ng b\u7883  qu\u7927  m\'ea t\'e2m \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean v\'e1ng \u273 \u7847 u, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0i thai, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'f3n v\u7873 , \'f4ng cam \u273 oan \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9 kia do t\u7897 c nu\'f4i d\u432 \u7905 ng, \'f4ng v\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n li\'ean h\u7879 . M\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 tha th\u7913  cho \'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0 do m\uc0\u7865  c\u7853 u v\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n c\'f9ng nhau \u273 \u7863 t, h\'e0i t\u7917  sinh sau c\u7853 u b\u7889 n th\'e1ng th\'ec do Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 \u7863 t. Tr\'ec Dung, h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n m\u7865  conTr\'ec Di\'ean dung n\u7841 p \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9 n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i kh\'e1c h\u7859 n l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n cam \u273 oan l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c. M\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 tin \u273 \u7891 n \'f4ng \u273 i bi\u7879 t vi\u7879 n th\u259 m m\u7865  con Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u7847 m truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n, M\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n c\'f2n ch\u7845 t v\u7845 n \'f4ng, v\u7851 n c\'f2n c\'e3i v\'e3 v\u7899 i \'f4ng; v\u7873  sau M\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f2n quan t\'e2m \'f4ng n\u7919 a, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7913 c xen v\'e0o, m\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n c\u361 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u7913 ng v\u7873  nh\'e0 c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng \'edt; n\u259 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\'e1u tu\u7893 i, Tr\'ec Dung c\'f9ng m\u7865  c\u7853 u chuy\u7875 n v\'e0o ch\u7911  tr\u7841 ch; n\u259 m c\u7853 u m\u432 \u7901 i s\'e1u tu\u7893 i, m\u7865  c\u7853 u v\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c ly h\'f4n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7853 u v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n c\u361 ng \u273 o\u7841 n tuy\u7879 t quan h\u7879 , c\u7853 u v\'e0 m\u7865  tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  dung n\u7841 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e3 dung n\u7841 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng xe d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7841 i m\'f4n Tr\'ec gia, l\'fac n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng y\'eau c\u7847 u mu\u7889 n \u273 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u m\'e0 y\'ean t\u297 nh ng\u7891 i trong xe ch\u7901 , d\'f9ng \'e1nh m\u7855 t \'fd b\u7843 o c\u7853 u c\u7913  y\'ean t\'e2m \u273 i v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7853 u tr\u7903  l\u7841 i k\u7875  t\u7915  n\u259 m m\u432 \u7901 i s\'e1u tu\u7893 i sau khi r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia. L\'e3o qu\u7843 n gia \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng ch\u7901  \u7903  c\u7917 a, th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n l\u7853 p t\u7913 c v\u7897 i v\'e3 d\u7851 n c\u7853 u t\u7899 i ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Vi\uc0\u7877 n S\u417 n n\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7855 p ch\u259 n b\'f4ng, m\u7863 t v\'e0ng nh\u432  ngh\u7879 , hai m\u7855 t nh\u7855 m nghi\u7873 n, nh\'ecn qua kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f2n s\u7889 ng hay \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng \'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t thanh ni\'ean \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng, d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i cao g\u7847 y, l\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung. Ngo\'e0i ra trong ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ai kh\'e1c, l\'e3o qu\u7843 n gia d\u7851 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7899 i r\u7891 i c\u361 ng nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i lui ra ngo\'e0i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng nghe th\u7845 y m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\'e0i r\u7845 t nh\u7865  c\u7911 a l\'e3o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean c\u7917 a nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i b\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 ng, n\'f3i th\u7853 t, c\u7853 u v\u7851 n duy tr\'ec c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c v\u7899 i hai cha con h\u7885 , chung quy b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t c\u7853 u. Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n kh\'f4ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 \'e3 nh\'fang tay v\'e0o s\u7921  ki\u7879 n kia, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng tin vi\u7879 c Tr\'ec Dung l\'e0m \'f4ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\u7855 m r\'f5.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'fac nghe tin t\u7913 c qu\u7843 n gia Di\u7879 p gia n\'f3i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7899  t\u7899 i chi\u7871 c t\'e0u h\u7887 a m\'e0u \u273 \u7887  kia, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7853 u s\u7869  th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7863 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ch\'ednh l\'e0 nh\u432  v\u7853 y, n\u7871 u ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, v\u7853 y s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \'f4m hy v\u7885 ng qu\'e1 l\u7899 n, c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 kh\'e1t c\u7847 u. Nh\u432 ng m\u7897 t khi \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i m\u7845 t \u273 i, s\u7869  nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 l\u7915 a g\u7841 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 gi\u7843 , \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 \u7843 o gi\'e1c, m\'ecnh v\u7851 n ch\u432 a m\u7845 t \u273 i, th\u7913  kia v\u7851 n c\'f2n thu\u7897 c v\u7873  m\'ecnh. Th\u7871  nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u ph\u7889 i h\u7907 p v\u7899 i c\u7853 u l\u7915 a m\'ecnh d\u7889 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, lu\'f4n d\'f9ng s\u7921  th\u7853 t n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng t\u7889 t \u273 \u7865 p c\u7911 a c\u7853 u v\u7873  cha \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 gi\u7843 , cho \u273 \u7871 n khi c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \'f4m b\u7845 t k\u7923  hi v\u7885 ng n\'e0o n\u7919 a m\u7899 i th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng khi nghe qu\u7843 n gia n\'f3i "C\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 l\u7847 n g\u7863 p cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ", c\u7853 u v\u7851 n l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n \u273 i g\u7863 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  c\u7853 u, c\u361 ng ch\u432 a tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  h\u7871 t hi v\u7885 ng nh\u432  ch\'ednh m\'ecnh v\u7851 n ngh\u297 .\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Nghe th\uc0\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n nh\u432  c\'f3 c\u7843 m \u7913 ng m\u7903  b\u7915 ng m\u7855 t, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean, trong mi\u7879 ng ph\'e1t ra \'e2m thanh "H\u432 ..\u432 ..".\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia kh\'f4ng n\'f3i b\u7853 y, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\'f3i qu\'e1 s\u7921  th\u7853 t, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y qu\u7843  th\u7853 t l\'e0 s\u7855 p kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \'f4ng \u273 \'e3 y\u7871 u \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i ra m\u7897 t c\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn \'e1nh m\uc0\u7855 t \'f4ng, \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n hai b\u432 \u7899 c. \'c1nh m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3 khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u h\u7891 i t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i khi c\'f2n nh\u7887 , Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ch\u417 i t\'e0u h\u7887 a, \'e1nh m\u7855 t chuy\'ean ch\'fa, \u273 i\u7873 m \u273 \u7841 m nh\'ecn \u273 \u7913 a con y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. M\'e0 l\'fac n\'e0y, \'f4ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Dung.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Dung tr\'e1nh sang b\'ean c\uc0\u7841 nh hai b\u432 \u7899 c, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 \u273 i t\u7899 i n\u7917 a ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, nghe th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a, g\u7855 ng s\u7913 c phun ra m\u7845 y ch\u7919 : "... Con..."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i \'f4ng h\u7887 i l\'e0: "M\u7865  con c\'f3 kh\u7887 e kh\'f4ng" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\'ecnh t\uc0\u297 nh nh\'ecn \'f4ng: "T\'f4i l\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c n\u259 m hai b\'e0 \u7845 y \u273 \'e3 \u273 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Vi\uc0\u7877 n S\u417 n nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, tr\'ean g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t v\'e0ng v\u7885 t ti\u7873 u t\u7909 y hi\u7879 n l\'ean n\'e9t bi th\u432 \u417 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng. Ng\'f3n tay kh\'f4 h\'e9o kh\u7869  \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\'fa \'fd t\uc0\u7899 i h\u7855 n tay tr\'e1i \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  ng\'f3n c\'e1i, b\u7889 n ng\'f3n c\'f2n l\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u h\u417 i h\u432 \u7899 ng l\'ean. \'d4ng \u273 ang t\'ednh, t\'ednh xem m\u7865  c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u273 i m\u7845 y n\u259 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  l\'e2y c\u7843 m x\'fac, trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y v\'f4 c\'f9ng bi ai. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u, bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n phong th\'e1i h\u7871 t th\u7843 y \u273 \u7873 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng sao b\'e2y gi\u7901  ch\u7907 t bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh b\u7897  d\u7841 ng d\u7847 u c\u7841 n \u273 \'e8n t\u7855 t, g\u7847 n \u273 \u7845 t xa tr\u7901 i; c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u v\'ec sao Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\'e0m ra v\u7867  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Vi\uc0\u7877 n S\u417 n l\u7841 i m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra, chuy\'ean ch\'fa nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, t\u7921 a nh\u432  \u273 ang ghi nh\u7899  th\u7853 t k\u7929  d\'e1ng v\u7867  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, m\'f4i \'f4ng gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t, ch\u7881  ph\'e1t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai \'e2m gi\'f3. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n qua kh\u7849 u h\'ecnh \'f4ng \u273 ang n\'f3i: "Con trai" .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng c\uc0\u7889  g\u7855 ng mu\u7889 n n\'e2ng ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7853 y k\u7873  s\'e1t v\'e0o Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m n\u7893 i \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n n\'e0y, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7843 nh n\'e0y, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i xu\u7889 ng k\u7873  g\u7847 n \'f4ng, sau \u273 \'f3 nghe th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u tho\'e1t ra hai \'e2m ti\u7871 t m\u417  h\u7891 : "\u272 i mau."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7855 c l\u7855 m quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn \'f4ng, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n bu\'f4ng th\'f5ng \u273 \u7847 u, hai m\u7855 t \u273 \'f3ng ch\u7863 t, \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e2u cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng \'f4ng n\'f3i l\'e0: "Con trai, \u273 i mau" .\cb1 \
