\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7899  t\u7899 i n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 m\'ecnh m\u432 \u7901 i s\'e1u tu\u7893 i, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n nh\u7889 t c\u7853 u ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a, \u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean trong n\'f3i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, "T\u7915  nay v\u7873  sau m\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 con tao. M\'e0y v\u7899 i m\u7865  m\'e0y mau ra kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y, \u273 \u7915 ng bao gi\u7901  quay v\u7873  n\u417 i n\'e0y n\u7919 a".\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p gia, mu\u7889 n b\'e1o cho Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca tin n\'e0y, mu\u7889 n n\'f3i cho ca ca bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh v\'e0 m\u7865  s\u7869  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia, mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i ca ca m\'ecnh n\'ean l\'e0m g\'ec b\'e2y gi\u7901 . Sau khi \u273 \u7871 n bi\u7879 t uy\u7875 n l\u7841 i ch\u7881  th\u7845 y r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u nh\'e2n vi\'ean y t\u7871  m\u7863 c \'e1o tr\u7855 ng ra ra v\'e0o v\'e0o ti\u7875 u l\'e2u. Ph\'fac b\'e1 n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t Tam c\'f4ng t\u7917  ph\'e1t b\u7879 nh \u273 \'e3 h\'f4n m\'ea, hi\u7879 n \u273 ang c\u7845 p c\u7913 u. C\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ngo\'e0i ph\'f2ng ng\u259 n tr\u7903  b\u7903 i c\'e1c nh\'e2n vi\'ean \u273 ang b\u7853 n r\u7897 n m\'e0 nh\'ecn h\u7855 n m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  v\u7851 n m\u7863 c chi\u7871 c s\u417  mi tr\u7855 ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, n\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t t\'e1i nh\u7907 t, v\'f4 thanh v\'f4 t\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian b\u7845 t l\u7921 c nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u. Ngay c\u7843  th\u7901 i gian \u273 \u7907 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  c\'e1o bi\u7879 t m\u7897 t c\'e2u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ph\u7843 i c\'f9ng v\u7899 i m\u7865  r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 i ngh\u297  t\u7899 i bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng g\u7863 p Tr\'ec Dung \u7903  H\u7913 a gia, Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i."T\'f4i khuy\'ean anh mau r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y." B\'e2y gi\u7901  nh\u7899  l\u7841 i, v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i t\'ecnh c\u7901  tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p v\u7899 i l\u7901 i n\'f3i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f2n l\u7841 i trong ph\'f2ng, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Dung. Tr\'ec Dung v\u7851 n l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m \u273 \u7913 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean, \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n ra qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u c\u7843 m x\'fac, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u432 \u7899 c, ch\u7881  nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean x\'e1c nh\u7853 n m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "Ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Vi\uc0\u7877 n S\u417 n b\u7897  d\u7841 ng kia, th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7889 ng qua \u273 \'eam nay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u. Tr\'ec Dung li\u7873 n m\u7903  c\u7917 a ra \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, b\'e1o tin v\u7899 i qu\u7843 n gia \u273 ang tr\'f4ng coi b\'ean ngo\'e0i, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a \u273 i v\'e0o, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "B\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\u7843 i v\'e0i ph\'fat n\u7919 a m\u7899 i t\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 G\'e3 l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c nh\'edu m\'e0y: "Sao anh c\'f2n ch\u432 a \u273 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\uc0\u7871 c Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \'e1nh m\u7855 t chuy\u7875 n sang Tr\'ec Dung: "V\'ec sao? C\'e1c ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'ec sao \u273 \u7873 u mu\u7889 n t\'f4i \u273 i?" Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, s\u7921  t\'ecnh c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n nh\u432  c\u7853 u ngh\u297  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c. Nguy\'ean nh\'e2n Tr\'ec Dung mu\u7889 n c\u7853 u \u273 i c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng c\u7853 u ngh\u297 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Dung kh\'f4ng tr\uc0\u7843  l\u7901 i c\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\'ec Di\'ean." G\'e3 g\uc0\u7885 i t\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean, "Anh c\'f3 bi\u7871 t tr\u432 \u7899 c kia v\'ec sao t\'f4i lu\'f4n c\u7889  \'fd mu\u7889 n g\'e2y kh\'f3 d\u7877  v\u7899 i anh kh\'f4ng? T\'f4i h\'e3m h\u7841 i anh, c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 \u7891  c\u7911 a anh, anh r\u7845 t c\u259 m gh\'e9t t\'f4i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? Anh ... h\u7853 n t\'f4i, \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, ch\uc0\u7881  im l\u7863 ng nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, b\'e2y gi\u7901  Tr\'ec Dung r\u7845 t k\u7923  qu\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i c\'f2n nh\uc0\u7899  r\'f5 tr\u432 \u7899 c kia ch\u7881  c\u7847 n b\u7855 t n\u7841 t anh, anh c\u7843 m th\u7845 y oan \u7913 c s\u7869  kh\'f3c, \u273 \'e1ng ti\u7871 c v\u7873  sau kh\'f4ng d\u7877  kh\'f3c v\u7853 y n\u7919 a, d\'f9 t\'f4i b\u7855 t n\u7841 t th\u7871  n\'e0o anh c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng kh\'f3c v\u7899 i t\'f4i, anh ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t \u273 i t\'ecm t\'ean kia." G\'e3 l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\u7899 p m\u7855 t, "C\'f3 ph\u7843 i v\u7853 y kh\'f4ng? Tr\'ec Di\'ean, n\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m anh kh\'f3c r\u7845 t d\u7877  d\'e0ng \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  khi anh tr\u7903  v\u7873 , ng\u7891 i xe Di\u7879 p gia r\u7901 i \u273 i \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3, t\'f4i kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 ngh\u297 ... Anh tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  kh\'f3c th\'e0nh b\u7897  d\u7841 ng g\'ec. Tr\'ec Di\'ean, con ma \u7889 m kia c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7887 a m\'e3n anh \u432 ? Hay l\'e0 tuy h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\'f3 c\'e1ch kh\'e1c gi\'e0y v\'f2 anh, khi\u7871 n anh kh\'f3c c\u7847 u h\u7855 n? Anh c\u7847 u h\u7855 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, kh\'f3c g\u7885 i h\u7855 n Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca? Hay l\'e0 \'f4ng x\'e3?" G\'e3 ti\u7871 n l\'ean m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \'e1nh m\u7855 t t\u7889 i \u273 en, n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i n\u417 i kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng v\u7915 a gi\u7889 ng kho\'e1i \'fd v\u7915 a gi\u7889 ng ghen gh\'e9t, l\u7841 i v\u7915 a gi\u7889 ng o\'e1n ph\u7851 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t c\'f2n v\u7863 n v\u7865 o.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'edu m\'e0y, lui v\uc0\u7873  sau m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t n\u7917 a nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7899 n ti\u7871 ng c\u7855 t ngang: "Im mi\u7879 ng." Nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Dung v\u7851 n b\u7845 t ch\u7845 p n\'f3i h\u7871 t l\u7901 i m\'ecnh mu\u7889 n n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Dung ti\uc0\u7871 n hai b\u432 \u7899 c v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, nh\'ecn g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t c\u7853 u: "T\u7915  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 n, trong t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 anh th\u7875  hi\u7879 n c\u7843 m x\'fac th\u7853 t s\u7921  v\u7899 i t\'f4i, d\'f9 l\'e0 anh c\u259 m gh\'e9t t\'f4i... h\u7853 n t\'f4i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao c\u7843 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7841 o m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i quay m\u7863 t qua n\u417 i kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn g\'e3. C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m qua tu\u7893 i tin lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n hoang \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y, hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  c\'e1i g\'ec g\u7885 i l\'e0 "Ch\u7881  c\'f3 anh th\u7875  hi\u7879 n c\u7843 m x\'fac th\u7853 t s\u7921  v\u7899 i t\'f4i"? Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n thi\'ean v\u7883  g\'e3, c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 t\u7921  m\'ecnh th\u7875  nghi\u7879 m, m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng r\u7845 t y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng con trai \u273 \u7897 c nh\u7845 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, l\u7847 n n\'e0y tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u7853 u m\u7899 i nghe n\'f3i m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'e3 qua \u273 \u7901 i n\u259 m n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c, nh\u432 ng t\'ecnh c\u7843 m y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng kia t\u7915  nh\u7887  \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 n kia \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 gi\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng li\u7871 c Tr\'ec Dung: "Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n v\'e0 m\u7865  c\u7853 u th\'ec sao? B\u7885 n h\u7885  th\'ec kh\'f4ng t\'ednh?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "M\uc0\u7897 t con r\u7889 i v\u7899 i m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i\'ean, anh n\'f3i xem n\'ean coi b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec?" Tr\'ec Dung c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, th\u7859 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi \'e9p Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7871 n v\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  lui \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch gi\u7919 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7881  c\'e1ch m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7899 i d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng v\u7851 n nh\u7871 ch l\'ean, "Nghe n\'f3i b\u7879 nh \u273 i\'ean s\u7869  di truy\u7873 n, anh n\'f3i xem c\'f3 ph\u7843 i t\'f4i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 i\'ean r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7917 a c\'e2u \u273 \u7847 u c\u7911 a g\'e3 khi\u7871 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\u7871 n s\u7855 c, gi\u432 \u417 ng m\u7855 t nghi\'eam m\u7863 t nh\'ecn g\'e3: "C\u7853 u c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng, " g\'e3 d\u7915 ng tr\'ean m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, "Anh v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u432 ? L\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 m\u7865  t\'f4i mang thai t\'f4i, l\'e0 do b\'e0 ta h\u7841  c\u7893  Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7893 ?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7849 m b\u7849 m. Th\u7913  n\'e0y Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  m\u7899 i \u273 \u7885 c trong truy\u7879 n v\'e0 xem tr\'ean phim, th\u7921 c t\u7871  ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p, cho d\'f9 l\u7899 n l\'ean \u7903  Tr\'ec gia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tin ch\u7855 c r\u7857 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 t\u7891 n t\u7841 i. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i Tr\'ec Dung l\u7841 i n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, th\u7913  n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'f9ng tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, cha c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng sai, ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\uc0\u7893 . M\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n b\'e0 \u273 i\'ean c\u7847 u m\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, v\'ec m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng y\'eau m\'ecnh m\'e0 d\'e2ng l\'ean thu\u7853 t vu c\u7893  b\u7843 n th\'e2n n\u7855 m gi\u7919  \u273 \u7875  ti\u7871 n v\'e0o Tr\'ec gia, c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i d\'f9ng c\u7893  \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n m\u7897 t con r\u7889 i v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ch\'ednh m\'ecnh l\u7915 a m\'ecnh c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i, th\u7853 m ch\'ed b\u7903 i v\'ec s\u7917  d\u7909 ng qu\'e1 m\u7913 c \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n m\u7845 t kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p, b\u7883  v\u7841 n tr\'f9ng ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  \u273 o\u7843 n m\u7879 nh m\'e0 ch\u7871 t, anh n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 i\'ean th\'ec l\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kinh ng\uc0\u7841 c nh\'ecn g\'e3, c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t Tr\'ec Dung \u273 ang n\'f3i m\u7865  g\'e3, h\'ecnh \u7843 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  kia hi\u7879 n l\'ean m\u417  h\u7891  trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u. M\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 y tu\u7893 i l\u7899 n l\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n, sau khi bi\u7871 t quan h\u7879  h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n gi\u7919 a nh\'e0 m\'ecnh v\u7899 i m\u7865  con Tr\'ec Dung, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u7853 u r\u7845 t c\u259 m gh\'e9t Tr\'ec Dung v\'e0 m\u7865  g\'e3, nh\u432 ng m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng r\u7855 p t\'e2m h\'e3m h\u7841 i m\u7865  con c\u7853 u nh\u432  g\'e3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong tr\'ed nh\uc0\u7899  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  kia th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng ra kh\u7887 i ph\'f2ng, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t t\'e1i nh\u7907 t, th\u7881 nh kho\u7843 ng g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i th\'ec v\u7867  m\u7863 t lu\'f4n l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng lu\'f4n l\'e0 th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  l\u7841 nh l\'f9ng \u273 \u7871 n coi th\u432 \u7901 ng. \u272 \'e3 nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  kia \u7903  trong \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 m\u7901  nh\u7841 t th\'e0nh m\u7897 t b\'f3ng d\'e1ng t\'e1i nh\u7907 t kh\'f4ng sinh kh\'ed, l\'fac n\'e0y t\u7853 p trung suy ngh\u297  m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  n\u7893 i h\'ecnh d\'e1ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7915  tr\'ean m\u7863 t Tr\'ec Dung lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7911 a m\u7865  g\'e3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Dung ti\uc0\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f3 m\'e0 ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t l\'e0 \u273 ang n\'f3i cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe hay ch\u7881  \u273 ang l\u7849 m b\u7849 m: "Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\'f4i lu\'f4n th\u7873  b\u7843 n th\'e2n tuy\u7879 t s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tr\u7903  th\'e0nh b\u7897  d\u7841 ng \u273 \'e1ng th\u432 \u417 ng l\u7841 i th\u7853 t \u273 \'e1ng bu\u7891 n nh\u432  b\'e0 ta, nh\u432 ng sau n\'e0y t\'f4i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n t\'f4i c\'f2n \u273 \'e1ng bu\u7891 n h\u417 n b\'e0 ta, ngay c\u7843  gi\u7843  d\u7889 i t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng chi\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ngay c\u7843  c\u417  h\u7897 i l\u7915 a g\u7841 t ch\'ednh m\'ecnh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3." H\u7855 n l\u7847 m b\u7847 m, thanh \'e2m c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng mu\uc0\u7889 n th\u259 m d\'f2 t\'e2m t\u432  Tr\'ec Dung, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u ch\u7881  \u273 \u7875  \'fd m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c. L\u7901 i Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  m\u7897 t th\'f4ng tin, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n nh\u7919 ng n\u259 m qua c\'f3 l\u7869  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n b\u7883  c\u7893  \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n, m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i thao t\'fang ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7921 c gi\'e1c l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Dung kh\'f4ng n\'f3i d\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng c\u7853 u tr\u7903  n\'ean kh\'f4 kh\u7889 c: "\'d4ng \u7845 y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra \u432 ? T\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i trong Tr\'ec gia c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra sao? Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869 ... kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai ng\u259 n c\u7843 n sao?"\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u259 n c\u7843 n?" Tr\'ec Dung ch\u7871  gi\u7877 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, "Tr\'ec Di\'ean, sao anh c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\'e2y th\u417  m\'e3i v\u7853 y ch\u7913 ? L\u7899 n l\'ean \u7903  Tr\'ec gia, s\u7889 ng trong ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh \u273 \'f3 m\'e0 anh v\u7851 n l\'e0 c\'e1i b\u7897  d\u7841 ng n\'e0y? Ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n? \'d4ng ta \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, cho n\'ean m\u7899 i mu\u7889 n th\u7915 a d\u7883 p thanh t\u7881 nh hi\u7871 m c\'f3 m\'e0 ngh\u297  m\u7885 i bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p \u273 \u432 a m\u7865  con hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i, th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i b\u7845 t k\u7923  li\'ean l\u7841 c n\'e0o v\u7899 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i. Nh\u432 ng anh n\'f3i xem v\'ec sao \'f4ng ta kh\'f4ng tho\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c? Anh ngh\u297  \'f4ng ta s\u7907  m\u7865  t\'f4i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n l\u7841 i g\u7847 n s\'e1t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng n\'f3i: "\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i. H\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7913  \u273 \u7845 u kh\'f4ng l\u7841 i, cho d\'f9 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vu c\u7893  thao t\'fang, c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i \'f4ng ta c\u361 ng l\'e0 con r\u7889 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia. Cho n\'ean anh c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ai s\u7869  quan t\'e2m, ai s\u7869  ng\u259 n c\u7843 n \u273 \'e2y? M\u7865  t\'f4i d\'e1m l\'e0m v\u7853 y v\u7899 i con trai tr\u432 \u7903 ng Tr\'ec gia, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\u361 ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n b\'e0y m\u432 u \u273 \u7863 t k\u7871  hay kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  to m\u7855 t, kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 l\u7841 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda thi th\u7875  tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng kia. An ngh\u7881  \u7903  \u273 \'f3 ch\'ednh l\'e0 cha c\u7853 u. C\u7853 u ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  ngh\u297  r\u7857 ng s\u7869  nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  Tr\'ec Dung m\u7897 t c\'e2u chuy\u7879 n nh\u432  th\u7871 . Nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o nghi\u7879 m ch\u7913 ng th\u7853 t gi\u7843  trong l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i, nh\u432 ng n\u7897 i t\'e2m c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 tin.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u \u259 n kh\u7899 p. Th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  Tr\'ec Dung r\u7845 t k\u7923  qu\'e1i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i l\'e0 th\u7853 t hay gi\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u7913 c ch\u7871  t\u7915 ng gi\u7885 t t\u7915 ng gi\u7885 t l\u7899 n l\u259 n xu\u7889 ng, \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7853 u \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng, quay sang Tr\'ec Dung: "V\u7853 y cha... \'f4ng \u7845 y l\'e0... l\'e0 th\u7871  n\'e0o..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, m\u7897 t c\'e2u n\'f3i ph\'e1 th\'e0nh t\u7915 ng \u273 o\u7841 n nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Dung v\uc0\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i g\'ec. G\'e3 b\'ecnh t\u297 nh nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, n\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e2uu kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan: "Anh l\u7841 i kh\'f3c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  m\u7855 t ra nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda g\'e3, Tr\'ec Dung th\u7843 n nhi\'ean n\'f3i ti\u7871 p: "Ng\u432 \u7901 i nu\'f4i c\u7893  ch\u7871 t, c\u7893  tr\'f9ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n, kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, t\'e2m c\u7893  sau khi ch\u7871 t, con r\u7889 i b\u7883  k\'ed g\u7917 i nu\'f4i c\u7893  tr\'f9ng \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean r\u7845 t nhanh c\u361 ng s\u7869  ch\u7871 t theo."\cb1 \
\cb3 "N\uc0\u7871 u anh mu\u7889 n \'f4ng ta \u273 i d\u7877  ch\u7883 u h\u417 n th\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7901  v\u7883  kia gi\'fap ti\u7877 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng." Tr\'ec Dung h\u7841  m\u7855 t, tho\'e1ng c\'e1i n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i, "C\'f3 l\u7869  c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\'f2n c\'f3, mau \uc0\u273 i \u273 i. \u272 \u7915 ng tin Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\'f4ng n\'ean v\'ec h\u7855 n m\'e0 \u7903  l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong c\'e2u \uc0\u273 \'f3, kh\'f4ng cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7901 i gian ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng g\'e3 \u273 \'e3 m\u7903  c\u7917 a \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i. \u272 \'fang l\'fac qu\u7843 n gia mang theo m\u7897 t nh\'f3m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i t\u7899 i, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u thu x\u7871 p h\u7853 u s\u7921  cho Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng t\u7841 i ch\u7895  nh\'ecn b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\u7853 n r\u7897 n, ti\'eau h\'f3a th\'f4ng tin trong l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i. \'dd t\u7913  sau c\'f9ng c\u7911 a g\'e3 l\'e0 b\u7843 o c\u7853 u \u273 i t\'ecm Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7901  h\u7855 n si\'eau \u273 \u7897  cho Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, Di\u7879 p gia tu Qu\u7927  \u273 \u7841 o, \u7903  ph\u432 \u417 ng di\u7879 n n\'e0y qu\u7843  th\u7921 c t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i th\'e0nh th\u7841 o, ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f2n l\'e0 gia ch\u7911  Di\u7879 p gia. Nh\u432 ng v\'ec sao g\'e3 l\u7841 i mu\u7889 n n\'f3i c\'e2u cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 \'f3? Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n l\'fac h\u7845 p h\u7889 i v\'e0 g\'e3 l\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n th\'fac gi\u7909 c m\'ecnh r\u7901 i \u273 i l\'e0 v\'ec sao? Tr\'ec gia c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec? N\u7871 u Tr\'ec gia th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n m\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n v\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \u7873 u ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, v\u7853 y t\u7841 i sao b\'e2y gi\u7901  b\u7843 n th\'e2n Tr\'ec Dung kh\'f4ng tranh th\u7911  th\u7901 i gian m\'e0 r\u7901 i \u273 i?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u. V\'f4 lu\u7853 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ph\u7843 i ra ngo\'e0i t\'ecm Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u432 \u7899 c, n\'f3i nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y cho h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i c\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7915 ng tin Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u432 ng hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean tr\'ean th\u7871  gian n\'e0y ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u tin t\u432 \u7903 ng nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. C\u7853 u tuy\u7879 t s\u7869  kh\'f4ng, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bao gi\u7901  c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i m\'e0 sinh l\'f2ng hi\u7873 m nghi Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
