\f1\b0 \cf2 Xe Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n \u273 ang ch\u7901  tr\'ean con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u7841 nh r\u7915 ng ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7841 i tr\u7841 ch Tr\'ec gia, \u273 \'e8n trong xe ph\'e1t ra \'e1nh s\'e1ng \u7845 m \'e1p, \u273 i t\u7899 i g\u7847 n c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y c\u7917 a s\u7893  xe gh\u7871  sau n\u7917 a m\u7903 , nam nh\'e2n m\u7863 c \'e1o cho\'e0ng d\'e0i m\'e0u \u273 en \u273 ang nh\'e0n h\u7841  nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t d\u432 \u7905 ng th\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7903  c\u7917 a xe x\'f4ng v\'e0o, \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\'e1nh tay h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m c\u7853 u, n\'e2ng c\u7857 m c\u7853 u \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y hai m\u7855 t \u273 \u7887  b\u7915 ng c\u7911 a c\u7853 u \u273 au l\'f2ng m\'e0 l\u7841 i g\u7847 n h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 th\u7871  n\'e0o? Ai l\u7841 i b\u7855 t n\u7841 t em?"\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 m\uc0\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m Tr\'ec Dung qu\u7843  th\u7853 t \u273 \'e3 \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \'fang, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'edch x\'e1c r\u7845 t th\'edch b\u7855 t n\u7841 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u432 \u7901 ng khi d\u7877  \u273 \u7871 n khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean hai m\u7855 t m\'f4ng lung kh\'f3c k\'eau \'f4m h\u7855 n l\'e0m n\u361 ng xin tha, h\u7855 n m\u7899 i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a th\u7887 a m\'e3n m\'e0 thu tay l\u7841 i, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u k\'e9o ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c ch\u7853 m r\'e3i d\u7895  d\'e0nh. Nh\u432 ng ch\'fat t\'ecnh th\'fa n\'e0y gi\u7919 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n l\u432 \u7907 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i n\'f3i, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7871 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c b\u7855 t n\u7841 t, h\u7855 n s\u7869  nh\u7899  k\u7929  trong \u273 \u7847 u, l\u7841 i t\u7921  m\'ecnh c\u7849 n th\u7853 n an \u7911 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, d\u7921 a tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Cha em m\u7845 t r\u7891 i." Gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i v\u7851 n c\'f2n ngh\u7865 n, n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7919  "Cha" g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ki\u7873 m ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. \u272 \'e3 m\u432 \u7901 i n\u259 m c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng g\u7885 i Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n n\u259 m m\u432 \u7901 i s\'e1u tu\u7893 i \u273 o\u7841 n tuy\u7879 t quan h\u7879  cha con r\u7901 i Tr\'ec gia, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\'f2n \u7903  Tr\'ec gia, b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u chuy\u7879 n, bi\u7871 t Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n c\'f3 l\u7895 i v\u7899 i m\u7865  con m\'ecnh, c\u7853 u r\u7845 t ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7889 i vi\u7879 c n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i \'f4ng, l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u g\u7885 i "Cha" hay "Ba" .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ra c\u7853 u thay \u273 \u7893 i x\u432 ng h\'f4, ch\u7881  xoa l\u432 ng gi\'fap c\u7853 u thu\u7853 n kh\'ed, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u7913 ng l\u7901 i c\u7853 u, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i th\'eam g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\uc0\u7875  l\u7841 i ng\u7855 t qu\'e3ng cho h\u7855 n chuy\u7879 n nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7915  ch\u7895  Tr\'ec Dung, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng m\u7897 t m\u7921 c y\'ean t\u297 nh l\u7855 ng nghe, ch\u7901  c\u7853 u n\'f3i xong m\u7899 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n x\u7889 c c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i l\'ean ch\'e2n m\'ecnh, \'f4m c\u7853 u m\u7863 t \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n m\u7855 t c\u7853 u: "Ngoan, \u273 \u7915 ng suy ngh\u297  n\u7919 a, ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i cho t\u7889 t, ca ca s\u7869  cho ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i \u273 i\u7873 u tra r\'f5 r\'e0ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u ch\'f4n b\'ean c\u7893  h\u7855 n, hai tay \'f4m eo Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng "V\'e2ng" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, hai m\u7855 t v\u7851 n \u273 \u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i ch\u7889 c l\'e1t, v\u7851 n gi\u7919  t\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, ca c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\'fap em ti\u7877 n \u273 \u432 a cha m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n kh\'f4ng, \u273 \u7875  \'f4ng \u7845 y c\'f3 th\u7875  ra \u273 i d\u7877  ch\u7883 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat? Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i \'f4ng \u7845 y b\u7883  vu c\u7893  thao t\'fang, t\'e2m c\u7893  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t n\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u7871 t theo. \'d4ng \u7845 y ra \u273 i kh\'f4ng y\'ean \u7893 n, em mu\u7889 n \'f4ng \u7845 y \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thu\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 "N\'ean l\'e0m v\uc0\u7853 y." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e1p, "Em nh\u7853 n \'f4ng \u7845 y, v\u7853 y \'f4ng \u7845 y c\u361 ng l\'e0 cha ta, ph\u7853 n l\'e0m con \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean ph\u7843 i ti\u7877 n nh\u7841 c ph\u7909  m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i xong nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  xe, ch\u7881  v\'e0o con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean tr\'e1i khu r\u432 \u768 ng n\'f3i: "Th\'e2n ph\u7853 n c\u7911 a ta b\'e2y gi\u7901  t\'f9y ti\u7879 n \u273 \u7871 n Tr\'ec gia si\'eau \u273 \u7897  nh\u7841 c ph\u7909  kh\'f4ng th\'edch h\u7907 p l\u7855 m, ch\'fang ta ti\u7877 n nh\u7841 c ph\u7909  \u7903  ngay ch\u7895  kia \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 n\'f3i b\u7843 n th\'e2n c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 v\'f4 th\u7913 c ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n tr\'e1i m\u7897 t c\'e2u l\u7841 i ph\u7843 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u "Nh\u7841 c ph\u7909 " trong mi\u7879 ng Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'e0i x\uc0\u7871  t\u7855 t m\'e1y, l\u7845 y t\u7915  trong c\u7889 p xe m\u7897 t t\u7853 p t\'e0i li\u7879 u d\u7909 ng thu\u7853 t, d\'f9ng di \u273 \u7897 ng soi \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i theo Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\'e0o trong r\u7915 ng. Xe Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quanh n\u259 m chu\u7849 n b\u7883  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i d\u7909 ng c\u7909  th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p n\'e0y, th\'e0nh ra gi\'fap gi\u7843 m b\u7899 t r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t m\u7843 nh \u273 \u7845 t tr\u7889 ng b\u7857 ng ph\u7859 ng r\u7897 ng r\'e3i th\'ec d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7883 u tr\'e1ch nhi\u7879 m c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i chi\u7871 u s\'e1ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7847 m b\'fat chu sa t\'e0i x\u7871  \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i, n\u7917 a qu\u7923  tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 l\u432 u lo\'e1t v\u7869  ra \u273 \u7897  vong tr\u7853 n, l\u7841 i d\'f9ng gi\u7845 y v\'e0ng phong b\u7871  c\'e1c m\u7855 t tr\u7853 n, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t thi ph\'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7915  t\u7915  nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t qu\u7923  b\'ean c\u7841 nh h\u7855 n, trong l\'f2ng m\u7863 c ni\u7879 m \u273 i\u7871 u v\u259 n \u273 \u7897  vong.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Trong r\uc0\u7915 ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean gi\'f3 n\u7893 i l\'ean, l\u7841 nh bu\u7889 t chui v\'e0o trong c\u7893  \'e1o, mang theo c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \'e2m u l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o. Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7907  run c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i, m\u7903  to m\u7855 t, nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\u7897 t h\'ecnh b\'f3ng m\u7901  \u7843 o \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda m\'ecnh, nh\'ecn d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\'ednh l\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7855 n" m\u7897 t m\u7921 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean, m\'f4i v\u7897 i v\'e3 m\u7845 p m\'e1y, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \'f3, th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng l\u7841 i c\'e0ng s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t m\'e0 g\u7841 t tay sang b\'ean c\u7841 nh ra hi\u7879 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn "h\u7855 n", nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean la l\u7899 n: "Cha, cha n\'f3i g\'ec? Con kh\'f4ng nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c!"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Vi\uc0\u7877 n S\u417 n nh\'edch th\'eam v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, c\'e1ch \u273 \u7897  vong tr\u7853 n tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng d\u7847 n d\u7847 n c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y r\'f5 kh\u7849 u h\'ecnh c\u7911 a h\u7855 n\'97\'97 \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y trong tr\u7853 n ph\'e1p \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean sinh ra m\u7897 t lu\u7891 ng l\u7921 c m\'e3nh li\u7879 t \u273 \u7849 y Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n ra xa, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n m\u417  h\u7891 , bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y g\'ec n\u7919 a... m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi tan bi\u7871 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n, "h\u7855 n" v\u7851 n lu\'f4n g\u7841 t tay v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'ean ph\u7843 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean tho\'e1ng c\'e1i ng\uc0\u7891 i s\u7909 p xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, quay sang tr\'e1i nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, ca n\'f3i xem cha em mu\u7889 n n\'f3i g\'ec v\u7899 i em? \'d4ng \u7845 y \u273 i c\'f3 thu\u7853 n kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "\'d4ng \uc0\u7845 y \u273 \'e3 v\'e3ng sinh r\u7891 i." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, \u273 \u7905  c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y h\'f4n tr\'e1n c\u7853 u, "\u272 \u7915 ng s\u7907 , b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, ca ca \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  b\u7843 o v\u7879  em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7847 u r\u297  \u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m nh\'e9t tr\u7903  l\u7841 i xe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7871 n d\u7921  \u273 \'e1m tang c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec v\u7889 n \u273 ang trong l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i, kh\'e1ch t\u7899 i r\u7845 t \u273 \'f4ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 t l\u7841 i l\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia n\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n ph\'fang vi\u7871 ng r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i Tr\'ec gia, h\u417 n n\u7919 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 o\u7841 n tuy\u7879 t quan h\u7879  t\u7915  l\'e2u, cho d\'f9 nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y kh\'f4ng \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean b\'ean c\u7841 nh gia ch\u7911  Di\u7879 p gia kia nghe n\'f3i l\'e0 b\u7841 n trai c\u7911 a ti\u7875 u th\u432  H\u7913 a gia, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\'f2n l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7903 ng t\'f4n Tr\'ec gia, th\'ec l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7913 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean nh\'ecn nh\u432  nh\u7919 ng kh\'e1ch kh\'e1c \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7871 ng, ch\u7853 m r\'e3i \u273 i l\'ean ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c d\'e2ng m\u7897 t b\'f3 hoa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\uc0\u7917  v\u7851 n \u273 ang b\u7871  quan, ngay c\u7843  con m\'ecnh \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean qua \u273 \u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ra. T\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7873 u do qu\u7843 n gia c\'f9ng c\'e1c gia \u273 \'ecnh con ch\'e1u Tr\'ec gia gi\'fap \u273 \u417 \u771  lo li\u7879 u, k\u7875  c\u7843  vi\u7879 c ti\u7871 p kh\'e1ch ti\u7877 n kh\'e1ch c\u7843 m \u417 n m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i x\'ec x\'e0o v\'ec sao kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y b\'f3ng d\'e1ng Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec thi\uc0\u7871 u trong mi\u7879 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i l\u7901 i h\u7887 i d\'f2 c\u7911 a c\'e1c kh\'e1ch \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7871 ng qu\u7843 n s\u7921  \u273 \u7873 u gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'f3i Tr\'ec Dung do \u273 au bu\u7891 n qu\'e1 \u273 \u7897  \u273 \'e3 ng\'e3 b\u7879 nh, hi\u7879 n \u273 ang d\u432 \u7905 ng b\u7879 nh trong ph\'f2ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  g\u7863 p kh\'e1ch, nh\u432 ng gi\u7919 a hai l\'f4ng m\'e0y l\u7841 i to\'e1t ra th\u7847 n s\u7855 c lo l\u7855 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Vi\uc0\u7877 n S\u417 n ch\u7871 t b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c k\u7923  t\u7917  thi th\u7875  v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 k\u7923  l\u7841 , hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i thi c\u7889 t ch\u432 a l\u7841 nh m\'e0 trong nh\'e0 tr\u7867  th\'ec b\u7879 nh n\u7863 ng li\u7879 t gi\u432 \u7901 ng, gi\'e0 l\u7841 i b\u7871  quan kh\'f4ng xu\u7845 t, to\'e0n b\u7897  Tr\'ec gia ngay c\u7843  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u ph\u7843 i nh\u7901  m\u7845 y t\u7897 c l\'e3o ch\u7911  tr\'ec. M\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i li\'ean t\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t t\u7897 c l\'e3o Tr\'ec gia v\'e0i ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7871 t kh\'f4ng minh b\u7841 ch, th\u7853 m ch\'ed ph\u7843 i d\'f9ng Tr\u7845 n H\u7891 n Kh\'fac m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\'f4n c\u7845 t, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i ngh\u7883  lu\u7853 n sau l\u432 ng Tr\'ec gia \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 ph\u7841 m ph\u7843 i Th\'e1i tu\u7871  g\'ec r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng nhanh ch\'f3ng, ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e1i \u273 i r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 tra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \'edt tin t\u7913 c t\u7915  c\u7843  tang l\u7877  l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n s\u7921  ki\u7879 n l\u7847 n n\'e0y, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u432 a t\u7899 i tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7883  \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7903 i phim truy\u7879 n ti\u7875 u thuy\u7871 t, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7895 i khi nh\u7855 c t\u7899 i thu\u7853 t vu c\u7893  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  ngh\u297  t\u7899 i cao nguy\'ean V\'e2n Qu\'fd, b\u7903 i v\'ec V\'e2n Qu\'fd nhi\u7873 u ch\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'ed, r\u7915 ng n\'fai nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7897 c tr\'f9ng, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c c\'f3 \u273 \u7911  \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n \u273 \u7883 a l\'fd \u273 \u7875  ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p n\'e0y. Nh\u432 ng thu\u7853 t vu c\u7893  m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung truy\u7873 n th\u7915 a l\u7841 i l\'e0 m\u7897 t m\u7841 ch kh\'e1c, ngu\u7891 n g\u7889 c t\u7915  Qu\u7923 nh Ch\'e2u hay c\'f2n g\u7885 i l\'e0 H\u7843 i Nam, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\u432 ng l\'e0 vu c\u7893  Qu\u7923 nh Ch\'e2u. Qu\u7923 nh Ch\'e2u \u273 \u7883 a th\u7871  trong cao ngo\'e0i th\u7845 p, b\u7889 n b\u7873  gi\'e1p bi\u7875 n, trong n\'fai d\u7877  n\u7893 i s\u432 \u417 ng m\'f9, gi\u7919 a n\'fai c\u361 ng l\u432 u truy\u7873 n m\u7897 t \'edt b\'ed thu\u7853 t, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p \u273 \'e3 d\u7847 n th\u7845 t truy\u7873 n, song m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung l\u7841 i ch\'ednh l\'e0 truy\u7873 n nh\'e2n c\u7911 a vu c\u7893  b\'ed hi\u7875 m nh\u7845 t Qu\u7923 nh Ch\'e2u. T\u7915  \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y xem ra l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i h\'f4m qua t\'e1m ch\'edn ph\u7847 n l\'e0 th\u7853 t, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f3 b\u7883  vu c\u7893  kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  hay kh\'f4ng v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i m\u7903  quan t\'e0i gi\u7843 i ph\u7851 u kh\'e1m nghi\u7879 m m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  x\'e1c nh\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7903  quan t\'e0i kh\'e1m nghi\u7879 m l\'e0 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ph\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7901 i hi\u7875 u c\u7893  thu\u7853 t Trung Nguy\'ean, mi\'eau t\u7843  t\u7917  tr\u7841 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e1p Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \'fang l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  h\u7841  c\u7893  c\u7897 ng sinh. Vu c\u7893  Qu\u7923 nh Ch\'e2u c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7863 c \u273 i\u7875 m ch\'ednh l\'e0 ch\u7911  nh\'e2n c\u7911 a c\u7893  sau khi ch\u7871 t c\u7893  tr\'f9ng c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u m\'e0 ch\u7871 t, m\'e0 lo\u7841 i c\u7893  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 y m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m nh\u432  th\u7871 , c\u7893  tr\'f9ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m nh\u7853 p v\'e0o tim ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841  c\u7893  h\'ecnh th\'e0nh h\u7879  th\u7889 ng c\u7897 ng sinh, c\u7893  tr\'f9ng v\u7915 a ch\u7871 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  r\u7845 t nhanh c\u361 ng s\u7869  suy ki\u7879 t m\'e0 ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7853 n tin t\u7913 c \u273 i\u7873 u tra g\u7917 i v\u7873  m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng kh\'e9p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7855 t. D\'f9 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7913 ng c\u7899  x\'e1c th\u7921 c c\u7911 a chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'e3 qua, trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n \u273 \u7883 nh Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n l\'e0 b\u7883  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u7843  nh\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  ly t\'e1n \u273 \u7873 u b\u7903 i v\'ec cha b\u7883  h\u7841  c\u7893  l\'e0m h\u7841 i. Th\u7911  ph\u7841 m l\'e0 m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung, nh\u432 ng m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t n\u259 m n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n tr\u7843  th\'f9 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  t\'ecm. M\'e0 theo \'fd trong l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3, ph\'eda sau chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'f2n c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang quan s\'e1t gi\'fap th\'eam d\u7847 u v\'e0o l\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7855 p x\u7871 p l\u7841 i t\u7915 ng \u273 i\u7875 m suy ngh\u297  trong \u273 \u7847 u, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  \u259 n kh\u7899 p m\u7897 t lo\u7841 t s\u7921  ki\u7879 n n\'e0y: n\u7871 u gi\u7843  thi\u7871 t r\u7857 ng nh\u7919 ng n\u259 m qua cha l\'e0 b\u7883  c\u7893  thu\u7853 t kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871 , m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi h\u7845 p h\u7889 i, c\u7893  tr\'f9ng ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i m\u7899 i c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\'e2y l\'e1t th\u7921 c s\u7921  t\u7881 nh t\'e1o l\'e0 th\u7853 t, nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\u7901 i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng "\u272 i mau" \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i cho c\u7853 u l\'e0 v\'ec s\u7921  an to\'e0n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u; t\u7841 m th\u7901 i ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7897 ng c\u417  ho\u7863 c nguy\'ean nh\'e2n, Tr\'ec Dung nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n th\'fac gi\u7909 c c\u7853 u r\u7901 i \u273 i c\u361 ng l\'e0 v\'ec mu\u7889 n t\u7889 t cho c\u7853 u; nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Dung n\u7871 u l\'e0 v\'ec mu\u7889 n t\u7889 t cho c\u7853 u, l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c t\u7841 i sao l\u7841 i d\u7921 ng l\'ean b\'e0n c\u7901  \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia nh\u432  v\u7853 y mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t c\u7853 u?\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y tr\u432 \u7899 c sau m\'e2u thu\u7851 n v\u7899 i nhau. C\'f3 hai c\'e1ch c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7843 i th\'edch, m\u7897 t l\'e0 gi\u7843  thi\u7871 t "Mu\u7889 n t\u7889 t cho c\u7853 u" l\'e0 sai, Tr\'ec Dung v\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n v\u7851 n mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t c\u7853 u; c\'f2n m\u7897 t c\'e1ch gi\u7843 i th\'edch kh\'e1c ch\'ednh l\'e0, mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i c\u7853 u l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'e1c, bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a ng\'e0y \u273 \'f3 \u7903  hoa vi\'ean H\u7913 a gia c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u sai l\u7901 i n\'f3i d\u7889 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Dung. M\'e0 t\u7841 m th\u7901 i ch\u432 a \u273 \u7873  c\u7853 p t\u7899 i Tr\'ec Dung, Tr\'ec Di\'ean hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng tin, ho\u7863 c l\'e0 n\'f3i kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n tin l\u7901 i n\'f3i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng kia c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n v\u7851 n c\'f2n mang \'e1c \'fd, cho n\'ean t\u7921  nhi\'ean c\u361 ng s\u7869  v\'f4 th\u7913 c b\'e1c b\u7887  c\'e1ch gi\u7843 i th\'edch th\u7913  nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean c\uc0\u7853 u ph\u7843 i t\'ecm Tr\'ec Dung h\u7887 i r\'f5 nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n g\'e3 bi\u7871 t, t\u7841 i sao nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n th\'fac gi\u7909 c c\u7853 u r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y, t\u7841 i sao ch\'ednh b\u7843 n th\'e2n g\'e3 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng nh\u7899  t\u7899 i b\u7897  d\u7841 ng Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u v\u7851 n h\u417 i e ng\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7853 u s\u7907  Tr\'ec Dung m\'e0 l\'e0 b\u7897  d\'e1ng \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7843  th\u7853 t c\'f3 \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f9ng trang l\u7913 a v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, th\'e2n ph\u7853 n hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  c\u361 ng \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n g\'ec c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i c\'f9ng, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng lo l\u7855 ng s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i. Cho n\'ean \u273 \u7875  ph\'f2ng ng\u7915 a v\u7841 n nh\u7845 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, nh\u7901  h\u7855 n l\u7841 i c\'f9ng m\'ecnh quay v\u7873  Tr\'ec gia t\'ecm Tr\'ec Dung m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7891 i xe \u273 i H\u7913 a gia t\'ecm H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y tr\u432 \u7899 c, t\u7915  r\u7845 t xa \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y trong s\u7843 nh ch\'ednh H\u7913 a gia c\'f3 kh\'f4ng \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang t\u7853 p trung \u7903  \u273 \'f3, m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7867  m\u7863 t \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng, \u273 \u7841 i b\'e1 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\'f9ng \u273 \u7841 i qu\u7843 n gia trong nh\'e0 \u273 ang c\u7889  g\u7855 ng tr\u7845 n an b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 i t\u7899 i, tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p m\u7903  c\u7917 a l\'ean xe, ng\u7891 i v\'e0o b\'ean c\u7841 nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe ch\uc0\u7841 y nhanh v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  ch\u7881  s\u7843 nh ch\'ednh: "C\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec th\u7871 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y nh\u7871 ch mi\u7879 ng: "M\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 thi\'ean s\u432  m\u7897 t ph\'e1i t\u7899 i tham gia l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i, m\'f4n ch\u7911  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  h\u7885  M\'e3, c\'f3 m\u7897 t con trai ch\u7915 ng v\'e0i th\'e1ng n\u7919 a l\'e0 tr\'f2n hai m\u432 \u417 i, t\'ean M\'e3 Thi\'ean, n\u259 m nay \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u7851 n theo tham gia nghi th\u7913 c t\u7871  t\u7921 . K\u7871 t qu\u7843  hai ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c M\'e3 Thi\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean m\u7845 t t\'edch, M\'e3 m\'f4n ch\u7911  m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u th\'fac gi\u7909 c H\u7913 a gia \u273 i t\'ecm con trai c\'f9ng b\u7885 n h\u7885 . C\u7853 u n\'f3i xem c\u7853 u ta c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh, n\'fai n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \u7875  ch\u417 i, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ch\u7915 ng l\'e0 ch\u7841 y ra ngo\'e0i ch\u417 i r\u244 \u768 i, v\u7853 y m\'e0 b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\u7841 i \'e9p \u273 \u7841 i b\'e1 ta nh\u432  v\u7853 y, b\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i t\'ecm kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u361 ng \u273 \'e2u c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i cha t\'f4i m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  \'f4ng n\u7897 i nh\'e9o b\u7855 t \u273 i h\u7895  tr\u7907 , may m\'e0 m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 c\'f2n ch\u432 a b\u7855 t t\'f4i \u273 i l\'e0m tr\'e1ng \u273 inh \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y \u273 ang t\u7893  ch\u7913 c l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i, l\u7841 i th\'eam Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n sau khi t\'e9 x\u7881 u \u7903  b\u7919 a ti\u7879 c \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c k\u7923  t\u7917 , H\u7913 a gia qu\u7843  th\u7921 c b\u7853 n t\u7889 i t\u259 m m\u7863 t m\u361 i lo li\u7879 u m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n. M\u7895 i c\'e2y m\u7895 i hoa m\u7895 i nh\'e0 m\u7895 i c\u7843 nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7895  vai H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y an \u7911 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7847 u kh\'f4ng kh\'ed Tr\'ec gia c\'f3 ch\'fat ng\u432 ng tr\u7885 ng, trong ph\'f2ng to\'e1t ra m\'f9i m\u7909 c n\'e1t l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o, linh \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n v\u7851 n c\'f2n m\u7903 , ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y ph\'fang vi\u7871 ng \'edt h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i h\'f4m qua. Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i c\'f9ng H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 i v\'e0o l\u7841 y m\u7897 t l\u7847 n r\u7891 i m\u7899 i \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  v\u7899 i qu\u7843 n gia mu\u7889 n g\u7863 p Tr\'ec Dung, n\'f3i c\'f3 vi\u7879 c mu\u7889 n nh\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i v\u7873  cha l\'fac sinh th\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u361 ng l\'e0 con ru\u7897 t c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, c\'f2n l\'e0 con trong gi\'e1 th\'fa, ch\'e1u \u273 \'edch t\'f4n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia kh\'f4ng th\u7875  d\u7883  ngh\u7883 , d\'f9 cho \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i, h\'f4m nay Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n qua \u273 \u7901 i, y\'eau c\u7847 u n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec b\u7845 t h\u7907 p l\'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia ch\'ednh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'eam h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i g\u7863 p Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n l\u7847 n cu\u7889 i, sau \u273 \'f3 gi\'fap lo li\u7879 u h\u7853 u s\u7921  cho Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, trong \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \'f4ng v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u273 i theo Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, b\u7903 i v\'ec th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n m\'e0 \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Dung m\u7897 t l\'f2ng trung th\'e0nh, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i m\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i v\'f4 c\'f9ng l\'e3nh \u273 \u7841 m. V\u7853 y n\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i \'f4ng c\u361 ng l\'e0 ng\u7919  kh\'ed xa c\'e1ch kh\'e1ch kh\'ed gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t vi\u7879 c chung, l\'e0m phi\u7873 n \'f4ng gi\'fap truy\u7873 n l\u7901 i cho Tr\'ec Dung, n\u7871 u Tr\'ec Dung th\u7921 c s\u7921  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7879 nh n\u7863 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 i l\u7841 i, c\u7853 u tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 i t\'ecm Tr\'ec Dung c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7897 i t\'e2m Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng tin c\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean "\u272 au bu\u7891 n qu\'e1 \u273 \u7897 " "B\u7879 nh n\u7863 ng li\u7879 t gi\u432 \u7901 ng", \u273 \'eam h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\'e1i ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng g\'ec, nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng c\'f3 s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng, sao c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u273 \u7893  b\u7879 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia l\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u v\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, cung k\'ednh d\u7851 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i sang s\u7843 nh b\'ean, sau \u273 \'f3 khom ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7873  ph\'eda H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y: "H\u7913 a thi\u7871 u gia c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7841 m th\u7901 i tr\'e1nh \u273 i m\u7897 t l\'e1t hay kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i v\uc0\u7899 i \'f4ng: "H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\'e0 b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u sinh t\u7917  c\u7911 a t\'f4i. \'d4ng c\u7913  n\'f3i th\u7859 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia l\u7841 i b\'e0y ra s\u7855 c m\u7863 t kh\u7893  n\'e3o kh\'f3 x\u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y th\u7845 y th\u7871  \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, ph\u7845 t ph\u7845 t tay v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, t\'f4i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i h\'edt th\u7903  kh\'f4ng kh\'ed tr\u432 \u7899 c, n\u7871 u b\u7885 n h\u7885  d\'e1m l\'e0m g\'ec c\u7853 u t\'f4i s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\'e1o cho Tam ca c\u7911 a c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7901  h\u7855 n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, qu\u7843 n gia \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean qu\u7923  s\u7909 p xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t kh\'f3c r\u7889 ng: "\u272 \u7841 i thi\u7871 u gia, nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u gia \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
