\f1\b0 \cf2 "Kh\'f4ng c\'f2n?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7863 p l\u7841 i, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u n\'e0y ngh\u297 a l\'e0 g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7905  qu\u7843 n gia \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, qu\u7843 n gia \u273 \u7913 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean k\u7875  l\u7841 i cho c\u7853 u ngu\u7891 n c\u417 n chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7889 n t\u7915  s\'e1ng h\'f4m qua b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'e2u, b\u7903 i v\'ec Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n m\u7899 i qua \u273 \u7901 i, thi th\u7875  v\u7851 n ch\u432 a h\u7841  t\'e1ng, Tr\'ec Dung th\'ec m\u7845 t t\'edch, t\u7897 c l\'e3o ph\'e2n ph\'f3 qu\u7843 n gia tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean che gi\u7845 u chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i kh\'e1ch \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7871 ng n\'f3i d\u7889 i r\u7857 ng Tr\'ec Dung b\u7903 i v\'ec cha \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean qua \u273 \u7901 i ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7843  k\'edch qu\'e1 l\u7899 n m\'e0 \u273 \u7893  b\u7879 nh n\u7863 ng, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \'e2m th\u7847 m ph\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i t\'ecm tung t\'edch Tr\'ec Dung.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng t\'ecm c\u7843  m\u7897 t ng\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia n\'f3i ng\'e0y h\'f4m qua sau khi Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n m\u7845 t, Tr\'ec Dung m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u273 i v\u7873  n\u417 i Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  b\u7871  quan, c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n t\u7921  m\'ecnh b\'e1o tang v\u7899 i L\'e3o th\'e1i gia, sau \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ai nh\'ecn th\u7845 y g\'e3 n\u7919 a. Kh\'f4ng ai d\'e1m qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  \u273 ang b\u7871  quan, ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m th\u7915 a d\u7883 p \u273 \u432 a c\u417 m h\u7887 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u v\u7873  tung t\'edch Tr\'ec Dung, l\u7841 i ch\u7881  nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u tr\u7843  l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Dung ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i sau khi ti\u7877 n v\u7883  kh\'e1ch cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7873 , qu\u7843 n gia t\u7921  m\'ecnh d\u7851 n theo hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec Dung qu\'e9t d\u7885 n, mu\u7889 n t\'ecm th\u7917  xem Tr\'ec Dung c\'f3 \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i \u273 \u7847 u m\u7889 i ho\u7863 c th\u432  t\u7915  g\'ec n\'f3i m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 \u273 i \u273 \'e2u hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec Dung l\'e1t s\'e0n g\uc0\u7895  m\'e0u v\'e0ng nh\u7841 t, ph\u7843 i ng\u7891 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t d\'f9ng tay lau, qu\u7843 n gia t\'ecm manh m\u7889 i xung quanh, m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m c\u7847 m kh\u259 n ng\u7891 i tr\'ean s\'e0n lau ch\'f9i. L\'fac lau \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean g\u7847 m gi\u432 \u7901 ng tay ch\u7907 t s\u7901  ph\u7843 i m\u7897 t v\u7853 t c\u7913 ng, thu\u7853 n tay k\'e9o ra cho qu\u7843 n gia nh\'ecn.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t h\u7897 p s\u7855 t phong k\'edn h\'ecnh tr\'f2n, ph\'eda tr\'ean c\'f3 m\u7897 t h\'e0ng l\u7895  tr\'f2n nh\u7887 , qu\u7843 n gia ra hi\u7879 u ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m m\u7903  chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p\'97\'97 b\'ean trong nhung nh\'fac \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i s\'e2u \u273 en \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t. Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'e3 ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n b\'ed thu\u7853 t c\u7911 a m\u7865  g\'e3, qu\u7843 n gia h\u7847 u h\u7841  g\'e3 nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t \'edt nhi\u7873 u, th\u7845 y c\u7843 nh n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t, b\u7843 o ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m \u273 \'f3ng chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p c\u7845 t l\u7841 i v\'e0o g\u7847 m gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m n\u7885  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y nhi\u7873 u s\'e2u ch\u7871 t nh\u432  v\u7853 y s\u7855 c m\u7863 t l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t l\u7855 m, \u273 ang v\u7897 i v\'e0ng n\u7857 m c\'fai xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  h\u7897 p s\u7855 t v\'e0o ch\u7895  c\u361 , ch\u7907 t nh\'ecn th\u7845 y trong g\u7847 m gi\u432 \u7901 ng h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i qu\u7843 n gia: "L\'fd gia, d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng Thi\u7871 u gia h\'ecnh nh\u432  c\'f2n c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'f3 l\u7899 n l\u7855 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia t\'ean L\'fd M\u7841 o, ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m trong Tr\'ec gia \u273 \u7873 u g\u7885 i h\u7855 n m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng "L\'fd gia".\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia lo l\u7855 ng tung t\'edch Tr\'ec Dung, kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u bu\'f4ng tha ch\'fat manh m\u7889 i n\'e0o, nghe v\u7853 y v\u7897 i n\'f3i: "Mau l\u7845 y ra xem l\'e0 c\'e1i g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m theo l\u7901 i du\u7895 i tay v\'e0o k\'e9o ra, n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n nh\u432  c\'e0nh c\'e2y kh\'f4 v\u7915 a kh\u7869  k\'e9o m\u7897 t ch\'fat v\u7853 t kia \u273 \'e3 k\u7865 t d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng, kh\'f4ng k\'e9o ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a. Ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m li\u7873 n \'e1p m\u7863 t xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, th\'f2 \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o trong mu\u7889 n xem r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 v\u7853 t g\'ec, b\u7883  m\u7855 c \u7903  \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7871 t qu\u7843  h\u7855 n nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\u7897 t \u273 \u7847 u ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4 qu\u7855 t, \u273 ang m\u7903  to con m\u7855 t tr\u7889 ng r\u7895 ng c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m s\u7907  t\u7899 i m\u7913 c h\'e9t to m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\u7891 m c\u7891 m b\'f2 ra ngo\'e0i, ch\u7881  v\'e0o g\u7847 m gi\u432 \u7901 ng run r\u7849 y nh\'ecn L\'fd M\u7841 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia c\u361 ng b\u7883  ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n l\'e0m ho\u7843 ng, t\u7921  m\'ecnh n\u7857 m \'e1p xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t nh\'ecn v\'e0o g\u7847 m gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u361 ng gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh kinh h\'e3i! Nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao \'f4ng \u273 \'e3 h\u7847 u h\u7841  nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m \u7903  Tr\'ec gia, th\u7845 y nhi\u7873 u hi\u7875 u r\u7897 ng, c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p m\u7897 t \'edt y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i th\u7853 t s\u7921  n\'ean r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n ra d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t b\u7897  th\'e2y kh\'f4, v\'ec v\u7853 y l\u7841 i g\u7885 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\'f9ng chuy\u7875 n chi\u7871 c gi\u432 \u7901 ng qua m\u7897 t b\'ean, \u273 em b\u7897  x\'e1c kia ra.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 M\'e0 s\uc0\u7921  t\'ecnh ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n L\'fd M\u7841 o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i \u273 \u7893  m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7841 nh. Qua ki\u7875 m tra, b\u7897  thi th\u7875  kia \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t g\u7847 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a thi th\u7875  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ai kh\'e1c, ch\'ednh l\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung m\u7899 i m\u7845 t t\'edch kh\'f4ng l\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u gia \'96 ch\'e1u \u273 \'edch t\'f4n th\u7913  hai c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia, c\u7845 t gi\u7845 u thi h\'e0i c\u7911 a ch\'ednh m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t g\u7847 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  n\'e0y \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0o c\u361 ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng k\u7923  l\u7841  qu\u7927  d\u7883 , sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 m\u7865  r\u7901 i \u273 i, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n \u273 \'e3 ch\'ednh th\u7913 c c\u432 \u7899 i m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung, th\u7853 m ch\'ed sau \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Dung c\u361 ng l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7915 a k\u7871  danh ch\'ednh ng\'f4n thu\u7853 n c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c l\u7847 n n\'e0y c\'e1c t\u7897 c l\'e3o kh\'f4ng d\'e1m t\u7921  \'fd quy\u7871 t, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e2n ph\'f3 qu\u7843 n gia tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean che gi\u7845 u chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e9p \u273 \u7875  truy\u7873 n ra tin \u273 \u7891 n, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i v\u7851 n n\'f3i Tr\'ec Dung \u273 ang mang b\u7879 nh kh\'f4ng th\u7875  g\u7863 p kh\'e1ch, \u273 \u7907 i Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  sau khi xu\u7845 t quan s\u7869  t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 o\u7841 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 th\uc0\u7875  b\u7903 i v\'ec Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng c\'f3 quan h\u7879  huy\u7871 t th\u7889 ng v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Dung, L\'fd M\u7841 o m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng gi\u7845 u gi\u7871 m, n\'f3i th\u7853 t m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia k\u7875  xong do d\u7921  nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 \u7841 i thi\u7871 u gia, c\'e1c t\u7897 c l\'e3o sau khi b\'e0n b\u7841 c xong n\'f3i thi th\u7875  Nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u gia kh\'f4ng th\u7875  gi\u7845 u m\'e3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  h\'f4m nay tr\u432 \u7899 c h\u7871 t m\u432 \u7907 n danh lo li\u7879 u cho ti\'ean sinh m\'e0 ng\u7909 y trang c\u7917  h\'e0nh m\u7897 t tang l\u7877  \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n cho Nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u gia, sau \u273 \'f3 ch\'f4n c\u7845 t Nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u gia. N\u7871 u \u272 \u7841 i thi\u7871 u gia kh\'f4ng v\u7897 i, l\'e0m phi\u7873 n ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng ti\u7877 n nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, h\u7841  m\u7855 t: "C\u7853 u ta v\'e0 t\'f4i lu\'f4n b\u7845 t h\'f2a, c\u361 ng ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c \u273 \'e3 mu\u7889 n t\'f4i \u273 \u7871 n, v\u7851 n l\'e0 th\'f4i \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean hi\u7875 u quan h\u7879  gi\u7919 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung l\'e0 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, nghe v\u7853 y ch\u7881  th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, kh\'f4ng c\u432 \u7905 ng c\u7847 u th\'eam.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  r\u7857 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean g\u7885 i t\'ean \'f4ng: "L\'fd M\u7841 o."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, ch\u7907 t nghe Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i r\u7845 t kh\u7869 : "Chuy\u7879 n \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia, l\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i t\'f4i sao?" Gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u7911 a c\u7853 u r\u7845 t b\'ecnh th\u7843 n, b\u7903 i v\'ec b\'ecnh th\u7843 n m\'e0 l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  ra s\u7921  ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 d\u7921  li\u7879 u tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843 n gia h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng, nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i b\u7845 t \u273 \u7891 ng xoay m\u7845 y v\'f2ng \u7903  \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng n\'f3i: "... T\'f4i ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t l\'e0 Nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u gia l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c qu\u7843  th\u7921 c \u273 \'e3 d\u7921 ng l\'ean m\u7897 t tr\u7853 n c\u7909 c, mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7841 i thi\u7871 u gia tr\u7903  v\u7873 , nh\u432 ng c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd h\u7841 i \u273 \u7841 i thi\u7871 u gia. Nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n kh\'e1c t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  kh\'f4ng n\u7893 i \u273 \'e1y l\'f2ng c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 nh, th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia c\'e1i d\u7841 ng kia, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n b\u432 \u7899 c v\'e0o r\'f5 r\'e0ng ch\'ednh l\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7917  c\u7909 c th\u7853 p t\u7917  v\'f4 sinh. Mu\u7889 n c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873 ? N\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\'ecnh c\u7901  g\u7863 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  k\u7923  qu\'e1i trong mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na kia, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t. Hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  n\u7871 u Tr\'ec Dung ngh\u297  c\'e1ch mu\u7889 n d\u7909  c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873 , v\u7853 y t\u7841 i sao sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u7853 u n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n hai l\u7847 n v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Dung, hai l\u7847 n g\'e3 \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng \u273 i m\'e0 l\u7841 i b\u7843 o c\u7853 u r\u7901 i \u273 i?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn qu\u7843 n gia n\u7919 a, quay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i kh\u7887 i, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y v\u7851 n \u273 ang ch\u7901  c\u7853 u \u7903  c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u v\u7899 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c r\u7901 i Tr\'ec gia tr\u7903  l\u7841 i H\u7913 a gia. L\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n b\u7919 a tr\u432 a, hai anh em H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y H\u7913 a H\'e2n gi\u7919  Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  l\u7841 i \u259 n c\u417 m. Th\u7883 nh t\'ecnh kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ch\u7889 i t\u7915 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng v\u7899 i t\'e0i x\u7871 , l\'e0m phi\u7873 n h\u7855 n \u273 i v\u7873  ngh\u7881  tr\u432 \u7899 c, bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u quay l\u7841 i \u273 \'f3n m\'ecnh, l\u7841 i g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i cho h\u7855 n bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh \u7903  l\u7841 i ch\u7895  hai anh em H\u7913 a gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u259 n c\u417 m c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u7891 n \'e0o \u7847 m \u297  ngo\'e0i s\u7843 nh ch\'ednh \u7903  s\'e2n tr\u432 \u7899 c, v\'f4 c\'f9ng h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n. H\u7913 a H\'e2n hi\u7871 u k\u7923 , nh\u7843 y ra ngo\'e0i nghe ng\'f3ng, m\u7897 t l\'e1t sau tr\u7903  v\u7873  b\'e1o tin v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y: "H\u7847 y, l\'fac anh v\u7899 i ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec \u273 i Tr\'ec gia, \u7903  \u273 \'e2y l\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n. M\'e3 m\'f4n ch\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y \u7891 n \'e0o nhi\u7873 u l\u7847 n, nh\u7901  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i t\'ecm con trai \u7845 y, b\'e2y gi\u7901  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c con c\u7911 a \'f4ng ta r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i l\'e0 \uc0\u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, n\'e9t m\u7863 t c\'f4 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  vui v\u7867 , Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 o\'e1n ch\u7915 ng vi\u7879 c n\'e0y kh\'f4ng \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean nghe H\u7913 a H\'e2n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "Nh\u432 ng l\'e0 t\'ecm th\u7845 y thi th\u7875 , \u7903  n\'fai b\'ean trong r\u7915 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y bu\'f4ng \u273 \'f4i \u273 \u361 a trong tay: "Sao l\u7841 i x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y? \u272 \'e3 bi\u7871 t nguy\'ean nh\'e2n ch\u7871 t ch\u432 a?" V\'e0i ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c L\'e2m Tr\u7909  \'96 con trai L\'e2m Nh\u7883  t\u7849 u \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7845 t t\'edch, sau \u273 \'f3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n thi th\u7875 , \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  v\u7851 n ch\u432 a tra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nguy\'ean nh\'e2n c\'e1i ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\'ednh l\'e0 k\uc0\u7923  qu\'e1i \u7903  \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y, " H\u7913 a H\'e2n n\'f3i, "L\'fac \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y thi th\u7875 , c\'f3 m\u7897 t thi\'ean s\u432  tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i h\u7885  T\u432 \u7903 ng sau khi th\u7845 y thi th\u7875  M\'e3 Thi\'ean \u273 \'e3 c\u7921 c k\'ec h\u7889 t ho\u7843 ng, M\'e3 m\'f4n ch\u7911  ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 n\'ean \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t h\u7855 n l\u7841 i. T\u432 \u7903 ng thi\'ean s\u432  c\u361 ng t\u7847 m tu\u7893 i M\'e3 Thi\'ean, ch\u432 a tr\u7843 i \u273 \u7901 i, m\u7899 i b\u7883  h\u7887 i hai c\'e2u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chi\'eau. H\u7855 n th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n hai ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c h\u7855 n v\'e0 M\'e3 Thi\'ean x\u7843 y ra m\'e2u thu\u7851 n \u7903  sau n\'fai, trong l\'fac k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \'e3 ra tay gi\u7871 t ch\u7871 t M\'e3 Thi\'ean, nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n s\u7907  M\'e3 m\'f4n ch\u7911  th\u7871  l\u7921 c l\u7899 n, lo l\u7855 ng b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n n\'ean b\'e8n d\u7913 t kho\'e1t ho\u7863 c l\'e0 kh\'f4ng l\'e0m, \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m th\'ec l\'e0m \u273 \u7871 n c\'f9ng, h\u7855 n \u273 \u7889 t thi th\u7875  M\'e3 Thi\'ean r\u7891 i ch\'f4n d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7897 t g\u7889 c c\'e2y, ngay c\u7843  h\u7891 n M\'e3 Thi\'ean c\u361 ng x\u7917  l\'fd s\u7841 ch s\u7869 , khi\u7871 n M\'e3 Thi\'ean ngay c\u7843  ma c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e0m, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\u7903  v\u7873  t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n b\'e1o o\'e1n. H\u7855 n v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  t\u7889 t t\'e2m l\'fd, kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  h\'f4m nay l\u7841 i t\u7853 n m\u7855 t th\u7845 y thi th\u7875  M\'e3 Thi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u7921 c k\u7923  ho\u7843 ng s\u7907 , k\u7871 t qu\u7843  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7883  l\u7897  t\u7849 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y nh\'edu m\'e0y: "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i n\'f3i h\u7855 n n\'f3i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7889 t thi th\u7875  M\'e3 Thi\'ean r\u7891 i sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a H\'e2n n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng sai. H\u7855 n n\'f3i h\u7855 n nh\u7899  r\u7845 t r\'f5 r\'e0ng, nh\u432 ng sau \u273 \'f3 v\'e0i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e1i c\'f9ng h\u7855 n \u273 i ra sau n\'fai \u273 \'e0o, \u273 \'e0o m\u7845 y c\'e2y xung quanh \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\u432 \u417 ng c\u7889 t nh\u432  l\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i. Hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ch\'ednh h\u7855 n c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 \u273 i\'ean \u273 i\'ean kh\'f9ng kh\'f9ng, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 th\u7853 t hay gi\u7843 , cho n\'ean t\'ecnh h\'ecnh tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t v\u7851 n \u273 ang h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n l\u7855 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean chen v\'e0o n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n, t\'f4i h\u7887 i c\u7853 u m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 c\u259 n c\u7913  theo t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng thi th\u7875  ph\'e2n t\'edch M\'e3 Thi\'ean ch\u7871 t khi n\'e0o kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng L\'e2m Tr\u7909  l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7901 i gian th\u7921 c t\u7871  t\u7917  vong s\u7899 m h\u417 n th\u7901 i gian m\u7845 t t\'edch kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a H\'e2n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "\u272 \'fang l\'e0 th\u7871 , sao c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec th\'eam, c\uc0\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i r\'e9t run. C\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'f3 m\u7897 t ph\u7887 ng \u273 o\'e1n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fd M\uc0\u7841 o kh\'f4ng n\'f3i sai, Tr\'ec Dung nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y qua n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i c\u7853 u c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y to\'e0n b\u7897  \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7843 i th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m Tr\'ec Dung c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t do nguy\'ean nh\'e2n g\'ec \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean mu\u7889 n khi\u7871 n m\'ecnh tr\u7903  v\u7873 , nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi m\'ecnh tr\u7903  v\u7873  th\'ec g\'e3 \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, m\'e0 ch\'ednh g\'e3 c\u361 ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \'f3, h\u417 n n\u7919 a \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n ra s\u7921  b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, cho n\'ean m\u7899 i li\'ean t\u7909 c b\u7843 o m\'ecnh r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'ednh g\'e3 kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 i, l\'e0 v\'ec g\'e3 bi\u7871 t e r\u7857 ng b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Dung \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ch\u7871 t, thi th\u7875  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh x\'e1c kh\'f4 gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t g\u7847 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7903 i nguy\'ean nh\'e2n g\'ec k\u7923  l\u7841  m\'e0 ch\u7881  l\'e0 g\'e3 qu\u7843  th\u7921 c \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t g\u7847 n m\u7897 t th\'e1ng. T\'ednh to\'e1n th\u7901 i gian, ch\'ednh l\'e0 th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m x\u7843 y ra s\u7921  ki\u7879 n th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia, hai c\u7843 nh s\'e1t m\u7845 t t\'edch. N\u7871 u l\u7901 i L\'fd M\u7841 o n\'f3i l\'e0 th\u7853 t, nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7843  thi\u7871 t Tr\'ec Dung d\u7921 ng l\'ean tr\u7853 n c\u7909 c \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia l\'e0 mu\u7889 n d\u7851 n m\'ecnh tr\u7903  v\u7873 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p th\u7847 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t qu\u7927  kh\'f4ng hay m\'e0 b\u7855 t c\'f3c m\'ecnh tr\u7903  v\u7873  ngay t\u7841 i \u273 \'f3, nh\u432 ng tr\u7853 n c\u7909 c ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng, bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh m\u7897 t t\u7917  c\u7909 c c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 a m\'ecnh v\'e0o t\u7917  \u273 \u7883 a, Tr\'ec Dung c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t trong qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'e0ng ngh\u297  c\'e0ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ph\u7887 ng \u273 o\'e1n n\'e0y c\'f3 l\'fd, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\'f2n v\'e0i chi ti\u7871 t c\u226 \u768 n b\u7893  sung, v\u7873  c\'e1i ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a cha, c\u7911 a L\'e2m Tr\u7909  v\'e0 M\'e3 Thi\'ean. C\u7853 u c\'f2n c\u7847 n thu th\'eam m\u7897 t th\'f4ng tin t\u7915  Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ng\u7891 i y\'ean n\u7893 i, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng li\'ean l\u7841 c t\'e0i x\u7871  t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i n\'f3i v\u7899 i H\u7913 a H\'e2n H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y: "T\'f4i ph\u7843 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  g\u7845 p c\'f3 ch\'fat vi\u7879 c, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7899  c\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'e0 mang theo b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e1p kh\'ed tr\u7915  t\'e0 b\u7843 o v\u7879  b\u7843 n th\'e2n. \u272 \u7907 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u nh\u7919 ng suy \u273 o\'e1n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u l\'e0 \u273 \'fang, nh\u432  v\u7853 y...\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u417 i n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u7903  l\u7841 i th\'eam \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
