\f1\b0 \cf2 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 ang ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7885 c s\'e1ch tr\'ean sofa, tr\'ean khay tr\'e0 \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t chung s\u7913  men r\u7841 n s\'e1ng l\'f3ng l\'e1nh, h\u432 \u417 ng th\u417 m tr\'e0 Thi\u7871 t Quan \'c2m l\u432 \u7907 n l\u7901  v\u7845 n v\'edt, nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7841 y x\'f4ng t\u7899 i bu\'f4ng s\'e1ch ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u: "Sao l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean v\u7897 i v\'e3 tr\u7903  v\u7873  r\u7891 i? Nh\u7899  ca ca?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ra s\uc0\u7913 c l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, b\'ecnh ph\u7909 c h\u417 i th\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tho\'e1ng c\'e1i l\u7841 nh m\u7863 t kh\'f4ng c\u432 \u7901 i n\u7919 a: "\'c0? V\u7853 y l\'e0 kh\'f4ng nh\u7899 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7889 t ru\u7897 t n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 kh\'f4ng nh\u7899 . L\'e0 em c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n mu\u7889 n nh\u7901  ca ca tra m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\'f3n tay Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7889 ng c\u7857 m, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\'f4m qua tin t\uc0\u7913 c n\'f3i ng\u432 \u7901 i nu\'f4i c\u7893  sau khi ch\u7871 t c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u c\u361 ng s\u7869  ch\u7871 t, 'Kh\'f4ng bao l\'e2u' n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 bao l\'e2u? V\'e0i n\u259 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Chuy\uc0\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i nguy\'ean nh\'e2n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean quan t\'e2m v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  n\'e0y, ch\u7881  \'fd b\u7843 o Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i h\u7855 n \u273 \u432 a, "G\u7885 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  h\u7887 i l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ean kia r\uc0\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 tr\u7843  l\u7901 i: v\'e0i n\u259 m ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, t\u7889 i \u273 a m\u7897 t th\'e1ng c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c s\u7869  l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t ch\u7871 t h\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t th\'e1ng. Th\u7901 i gian v\u7915 a kh\u7899 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7902  ch\u7895  n\'e0y, n\u417 i c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432  ba d\'f2ng t\u7897 c h\u7885  Tr\'ec, Di\u7879 p, H\u7913 a \u7849 n c\u432  tr\'ean n\'fai \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921  \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia. Ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t ch\u7871 t bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927 , m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i xung quanh b\u7885 n h\u7885 , th\u7853 m ch\'ed l\'e0 ch\'ednh h\u7885  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i hay qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e2m Tr\uc0\u7909 , M\'e3 Thi\'ean, Tr\'ec Dung, \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t tr\u432 \u7899 c khi m\u7845 t t\'edch. L\'e2m Tr\u7909  b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\u7845 t t\'edch l\'e0 v\'ec khi \u273 \'f3 h\u7891 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t kh\'f4ng r\'f5 nguy\'ean nh\'e2n; tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p M\'e3 Thi\'ean v\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung c\u361 ng v\u7853 y, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 h\u7891 n tan bi\u7871 n s\u7841 ch s\u7869 , ngay c\u7843  ma qu\u7927  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  th\'e0nh m\u7899 i b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\u7845 t t\'edch, ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n thi th\u7875  b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 n n\u7919 a s\u7921  t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a lo\u7841 i qu\u7927  kh\'ed gi\u7889 ng th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia s\u7869  l\'e0m x\'e1o tr\u7897 n ph\'e1n \u273 o\'e1n c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885 , che gi\u7845 u s\u7921  th\u7853 t n\'e0y. Thi th\u7875  c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, v\u7883  T\u432 \u7903 ng thi\'ean s\u432  cho l\'e0 m\'ecnh l\u7905  tay gi\u7871 t ch\u7871 t M\'e3 Thi\'ean th\u7853 t ra c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng gi\u7871 t ch\u7871 t M\'e3 Thi\'ean, b\u7903 i v\'ec kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7871 t m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, h\u7855 n ch\u7881  th\u7853 t s\u7921  di\u7879 t h\u7891 n M\'e3 Thi\'ean, k\u7875  c\u7843  vi\u7879 c x\u7917  l\'fd thi th\u7875  kh\'f4ng t\u7891 n t\u7841 i c\u7911 a M\'e3 Thi\'ean c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n do t\u7847 ng m\'ea ch\u432 \u7899 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y g\'e2y ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\'e0 b\'e0 v\'e0 con g\'e1i \'f4ng ch\u7911  nh\'e0 tr\u7885  \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia, n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c khe h\u7903  ph\'e1 ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m ch\u7871 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y ch\'ednh l\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung. D\u432 \u7899 i t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a m\'ea ch\u432 \u7899 ng, g\'e3 \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n gi\u7845 u d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng g\'e3 ch\'ednh l\'e0 thi th\u7875  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, c\u417  h\u7897 i \u273 \u7875  g\'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n h\u7859 n l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c kia. L\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7905 ng c\u7893 , khi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh li\'ean t\u7909 c ch\u7871 t, c\'f3 l\u7869  g\'e3 \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra s\u7921  b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n nh\uc0\u7899  l\'fac m\'ecnh h\u7887 i Tr\'ec Dung v\u7873  c\'e1i ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a cha, \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \'e3 tr\u7843  l\u7901 i \'97\'97 ""Ng\u432 \u7901 i nu\'f4i c\u7893  ch\u7871 t, c\u7893  tr\'f9ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n, kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u c\u361 ng s\u7869  ch\u7871 t, t\'e2m c\u7893  sau khi ch\u7871 t, con r\u7889 i b\u7883  k\'ed g\u7917 i nu\'f4i c\u7893  tr\'f9ng \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean r\u7845 t nhanh c\u361 ng s\u7869  ch\u7871 t theo."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n cho r\u7857 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7905 ng c\u7893  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t trong l\u7901 i g\'e3 n\'f3i l\'e0 m\u7865  g\'e3. Nh\u432 ng hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i, ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7905 ng c\u7893  h\u7859 n l\'e0 ch\'ednh b\u7843 n th\'e2n g\'e3, tr\u432 \u7899 c khi qua \u273 \u7901 i m\u7865  g\'e3 \u273 \'e3 giao l\u7841 i c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh cho Tr\'ec Dung, bao g\u7891 m c\u7843  c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c thao t\'fang Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n. M\'e0 sau khi Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7887  m\'ecnh ngo\'e0i \'fd mu\u7889 n, nh\u7919 ng c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c kia m\u7899 i l\'e0 "Kh\'f4ng ai ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n" . Cho n\'ean th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m cha tr\'fat h\u417 i th\u417 \u777  cu\u244 \u769 i c\'f9ng, Tr\'ec Dung c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 hi\u7875 u r\'f5 r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t. G\'e3 c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng trong \u273 \'f3 n\'ean m\u7899 i c\u7889  \'fd b\u7843 o Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\'ecm Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7901  ti\u7877 n \u273 \u432 a Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, b\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 m Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i v\'e3ng sinh m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c b\u7883  nh\u7889 t \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y nh\u432  g\'e3.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec sao Tr\'ec Dung kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi si\'eau \u273 \u7897  v\'e3ng sinh cho b\u7843 n th\'e2n? Sau khi bi\u7871 t r\'f5 m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, g\'e3 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n g\'ec m\'e0 cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\'ec sao l\u7841 i tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p khi\u7871 n g\'e3 h\u7891 n phi ph\'e1ch t\'e1n?\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean vang l\'ean, ti\u7871 ng chu\'f4ng c\u259 \u769 t \u273 \u432 \u769 t d\'f2ng suy ngh\u297  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, c\u7853 u nh\'ecn m\'e0n h\'ecnh, l\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m g\u7885 i t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ti\uc0\u7871 p \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, gi\u7885 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\'e1ch mu\'f4n s\'f4ng ngh\'ecn n\'fai truy\u7873 n t\u7899 i: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , c\u7853 u mau v\u7873  nh\'e0 m\u7897 t chuy\u7871 n \u273 i, bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean t\'e9 x\u7881 u, b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 ang \u7903  trong vi\u7879 n v\u7851 n ch\u432 a t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c xa kh\'f4ng c\u7913 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\u7917 a g\u7847 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac \u273 i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i s\u7889  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u259 m s\'f3c ngo\u7841 i, n\'f3i cho b\'e0 bi\u7871 t n\u7871 u g\u7863 p vi\u7879 c g\u7845 p th\'ec li\'ean l\u7841 c T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nh\u7901  gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 . Bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean t\'e9 x\u7881 u, b\'e0 d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh th\u7871  c\u7845 p b\'e1ch \u273 \'e3 g\u7885 i cho T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  tr\u7907  gi\'fap c\u7911 a h\u7855 n thu x\u7871 p \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n ch\u7895  \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean, l\'fac n\'e0y T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian th\'f4ng b\'e1o cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c s\u7919 ng s\u7901 . M\u7895 i t\u7889 i sau khi \u259 n c\u417 m xong c\u7853 u \u273 \u7873 u d\'e0nh th\u7901 i gian g\u7885 i cho ngo\u7841 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn ra quy lu\u7853 t \u273 \'f3, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\u7889  \'fd ch\u7885 n th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y tr\'eau ch\u7885 c c\u7853 u, ch\'ednh l\'e0 d\'e1m ch\u7855 c l\'fac c\u7853 u v\'e0 \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o ph\u7843 n kh\'e1ng. T\u7889 i qua l\'fac g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\u7851 n c\'f2n r\u7845 t kh\u7887 e, t\'e1m chuy\u7879 n con trai l\'e3o Tr\u432 \u417 ng hay t\u7853 p th\u7875  d\u7909 c c\'f9ng \'f4ng m\u7899 i l\'ean ch\u7913 c, ch\'e1u g\'e1i l\'e3o H\u7891  \u273 o\u7841 t gi\u7843 i r\u7891 i th\'eam m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n l\'f4ng g\'e0 v\u7887  t\u7887 i, ai ng\u7901  h\'f4m nay l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7883  ng\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m s\u7869  c\u7889  g\u7855 ng h\u7871 t s\u7913 c mau ch\'f3ng tr\u7903  v\u7873 , c\u361 ng nh\u7901  c\u7853 y h\u7855 n ch\u259 m s\'f3c \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac m\'ecnh v\u7873 , sau \u273 \'f3 c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7897 i dung cu\u7897 c g\u7885 i, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ng\'e2y ng\u7889 c \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, b\u7897  d\u7841 ng lo l\u7855 ng b\u7845 t l\u7921 c kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y \'f4m c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng c\u7841 nh m\'ecnh, tr\u7845 n an n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, ca ca l\u7853 p t\u7913 c an b\'e0i xe \u273 \u432 a em v\u7873  th\u259 m \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i \'f4m c\'e1nh tay h\u7855 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \u273 i c\'f9ng em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? Ca c\'f9ng em tr\u7903  v\u7873 ." N\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n ph\u7847 n sau trong thanh \'e2m \u273 \'e3 mang theo \'fd t\u7913  n\u259 n n\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ca ca c\'f3 chuy\uc0\u7879 n \u7903  Di\u7879 p gia ph\u7843 i x\u7917  l\'fd, t\u7841 m th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi xoa t\'f3c c\u7853 u, n\'e9t m\u7863 t \u273 i\u7873 m t\u297 nh, "Qua m\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian ng\u7855 n n\u7919 a ca ca s\u7869  \u273 i t\'ecm em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? Thu\u7853 n ti\u7879 n \u273 \'f3n ti\u7875 u A Di\'ean c\u7911 a ta tr\u7903  v\u7873 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7895 ng d\u432 ng x\u7865 t qua m\u7897 t \'fd ngh\u297 \'97\'97 Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca qu\u7843  nhi\'ean l\'e0 mu\u7889 n c\u7853 u \u7903  l\u7841 i ch\u7895  n\'e0y c\'f9ng h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "N\uc0\u7871 u A Di\'ean kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7907 i tr\'ean n\'fai, ch\u7901  ta gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t xong chuy\u7879 n Di\u7879 p gia s\u7869  \u273 i t\'ecm em, sau n\'e0y lu\'f4n \u7903  c\'f9ng em, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?" T\u7921 a h\u7891  nh\'ecn ra Tr\'ec Di\'ean gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh trong nh\'e1y m\u7855 t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7853 p t\u7913 c b\u7893  sung, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng xanh b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, mang theo \'f4n nhu tr\u432 \u7899 c sau nh\u432  m\u7897 t ch\u7881  c\'f3 khi \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, mu\u7889 n n\'f3i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i th\'f4i, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ch\u7881  \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\'e1nh tay h\u7855 n: "Ca ca c\'f2n nh\u7899  Tr\'ec Dung kh\'f4ng? H\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i, \'fd em l\'e0 h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t kho\u7843 ng m\u7897 t th\'e1ng tr\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i, 'Tr\'ec Dung' ch\'fang ta g\u7863 p l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i. Ca ca c\'f3 nh\u7899  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, ng\u432 \u7901 i em t\u7915 ng k\u7875  c\'f9ng em \u273 i l\'e0m nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  k\u7871 t qu\u7843  g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i qu\u7927  th\'f4n kh\'f4ng? Em nghi ng\u7901  n\'fai n\'e0y x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n gi\u7889 ng th\'f4n \u273 \'f3, ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u ch\u432 a hay bi\u7871 t g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i r\uc0\u7845 t v\u7897 i, c\'f2n \u273 \u432 a ra L\'e2m Tr\u7909  v\'e0 M\'e3 Thi\'ean l\'e0m b\u7857 ng ch\u7913 ng ch\u7913 ng minh \'fd ngh\u297  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i ch\u7881  nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, vu\u7889 t t\'f3c c\u7853 u n\'f3i: "\u7914 , Tr\'ec Dung, L\'e2m Tr\u7909 , M\'e3 Thi\'ean l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, cho n\'ean A Di\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p b\u7885 n h\u7885  khi \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, c\'f2n n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i h\u7885  n\'ean s\u7907  h\'e3i \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  s\u7907 , " Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'f4m c\'e1nh tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7855 c, "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, em r\u7845 t lo cho ca ca, ca ca l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i em lo l\u7855 ng nh\u7845 t \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y. Ch\'fang ta c\u259 n b\u7843 n ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i hay qu\u7927 , s\u7869  r\u7845 t d\u7877  b\u7883  gi\u7871 t, th\u7853 m ch\'ed sau khi ch\u7871 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  l\'e0 m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  th\'f4n d\'e2n \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7913 a nh\u7887  ng\u7889 c." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn b\u7897  d\u7841 ng c\u7853 u lo l\u7855 ng s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t nh\'ecn m\'ecnh, nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7863 t c\u7853 u ng\u7891 i tr\'ean sofa c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4n c\u7853 u, m\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u m\u7899 i bu\'f4ng ra, "Em \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean ca ca l\'e0m g\'ec \u432 ? Sao c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi du\u7895 i ng\'f3n c\'e1i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng vu\u7889 t ve b\u7901  m\'f4i b\u7883  ch\'e0 \u273 \u7841 p \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7887  l\'ean, \'e1nh m\u7855 t s\'e2u th\u7859 m: "Y\'ean t\'e2m, ca ca x\u7917  l\'fd xong chuy\u7879 n n\u417 i n\'e0y s\u7869  \u273 i t\'ecm em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 gia ch\u7911  Di\u7879 p gia, tuy r\u7857 ng c\u417  th\u7875  kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 e nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh xung quanh l\u7921 c kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  r\u7845 t m\u7841 nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean tin t\u432 \u7903 ng n\u259 ng l\u7921 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n nay lu\'f4n c\'f3 d\u7921  t\'ednh, c\u361 ng th\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 u th\'eam n\u7919 a. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i n\'f3i suy \u273 o\'e1n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh cho hai anh em H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y H\u7913 a H\'e2n bi\u7871 t, n\u7871 u m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  nh\u432  c\u7853 u ngh\u297 , v\u7853 y t\'ecnh h\'ecnh b\'e2y gi\u7901  th\u7853 t s\u7921  r\u7845 t t\u7879 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u lo \u7903  qu\'e1 g\u7847 n s\u7869  l\'e0m \u7891 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean \u273 i qua m\u7897 t b\'ean g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i nghe m\'e1y. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a nh\u7845 n ng\u7855 t chu\u7849 n b\u7883  g\u7885 i l\u7841 i, ch\u7907 t th\u7845 y qu\u7843 n gia \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n, thi l\u7877  v\u7899 i c\u7853 u v\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, sau \u273 \'f3 quay v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i: "Tam gia, Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  xu\u7845 t quan, ph\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y th\u7881 nh Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, n\'f3i mu\u7889 n g\u7863 p Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe v\uc0\u7853 y l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ng\'e2y ng\u432 \u7901 i, ngay sau \u273 \'f3 v\'f4 s\u7889  o\'e1n gi\u7853 n kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 x\'f4ng l\'ean \u273 \u7847 u. C\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i v\u7883  t\u7893  ph\u7909  n\'e0y m\u7897 t c\'e2u, n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 t\u7841 i sao mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7863 t t\'ean "Dung" cho Tr\'ec Dung, r\'f5 r\'e0ng ng\u7847 m l\'e0m ch\u7895  d\u7921 a cho b\u7885 n h\u7885 ; r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \'f4ng c\'f3 bi\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung h\u7841  c\u7893  cha hay kh\'f4ng, n\u7871 u nh\u432  bi\u7871 t r\'f5, v\'ec sao kh\'f4ng ng\u259 n c\u7843 n, tr\u417  m\u7855 t nh\'ecn con trai b\u7883  thao t\'fang n\u7917 a \u273 \u7901 i, cho \u273 \u7871 n khi v\'ec th\u7871  m\'e0 b\u7887  m\u7841 ng. Ch\u7881  l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec tham lam c\u7893  thu\u7853 t b\'ed truy\u7873 n m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung mang \u273 \u7871 n, hay l\'e0 c\u259 m gi\u7853 n cha n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 kh\u259 ng kh\u259 ng c\u7889  ch\u7845 p b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n l\u7845 y m\u7865  v\u7873 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng lu\'f4n cho r\u7857 ng \'f4ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  ch\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng t\'e1n th\'e0nh h\'f4n s\u7921  c\u7911 a cha m\u7865  n\'ean m\u7899 i mu\u7889 n l\'e0m th\u7871 , b\'e2y gi\u7901  ngh\u297  l\u7841 i, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i \u273 \u7913 ng im t\u7841 i ch\u7895  kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i nh\u432  nh\'ecn ra \'fd ngh\u297  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, b\'ecnh th\u7843 n n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean mu\u7889 n g\u7863 p th\'ec \u273 i g\u7863 p, c\'f3 g\'ec mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i th\'ec c\u7913  h\u7887 i. C\'f3 ca ca \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m g\'e2y kh\'f3 d\u7877  em. Hi\u7875 u r\'f5 m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n r\u7891 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  xem \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i c\u361 ng an t\'e2m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn v\uc0\u7873  ph\'eda h\u7855 n, m\u7845 p m\'e1y m\'f4i g\u7853 t g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Song c\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ng\u7891 i xe Tr\'ec gia ph\'e1i t\u7899 i \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi cho t\'e0i x\u7871  l\'e1i xe c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7915 a l\'ean xe th\'ec H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y g\u7885 i l\u7841 i cho c\u7853 u: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec th\u7871 ? \u272 \'fang l\'fac t\'f4i v\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t tin, \u273 ang mu\u7889 n b\'e1o cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t th\'ec th\u7845 y cu\u7897 c g\u7885 i nh\u7905  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'e1p di \uc0\u273 \u7897 ng l\u7841 i g\u7847 n h\u417 n: "C\u7853 u n\'f3i tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  L\'e2m Tr\u7909  \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean m\u7845 t t\'edch kh\'f4ng? B\'e1c c\u7843  nh\'e0 t\'f4i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng \u273 i\u7873 u tra nguy\'ean nh\'e2n h\u7855 n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean h\u7891 n phi ph\'e1ch t\'e1n, sau \u273 \'f3 d\'f9ng b\'ed ph\'e1p t\'ecm h\u7891 n th\'ec ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n n\u417 i kh\'ed t\u7913 c cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7911 a h\u7891 n h\u7855 n bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t l\'e0 \u7903  Tr\'ec gia, g\u7847 n n\u417 i t\u7893  ph\u7909  c\u7853 u b\u7871  quan."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o v\u7899 i th\'f4ng tin n\'e0y. L\u7869  ra n\u7871 u c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t r\'f5 Tr\'ec gia c\'f3 c\u7893  qu\'e1i, n\u417 i n\'e0y c\u361 ng c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 , tin t\u7913 c n\'e0y ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\u7885 ng r\u417 m cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng \u273 \'e8 ch\u7871 t con l\u7841 c \u273 \'e0, khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m n\u7919 a, mang theo H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\'f9ng H\u7913 a H\'e2n quay \u273 \u7847 u b\u7887  ch\u7841 y, tr\u7903  v\u7873  ch\u259 m s\'f3c \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, ch\u7901  Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca x\u7917  l\'fd xong m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n s\u7869  \u273 i t\'ecm m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 kh\'edch l\u7879  c\u7853 u \u273 i \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t, kh\'edch l\u7879  c\u7853 u t\'ecm hi\u7875 u ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng, n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n s\u7907 , c\'f3 h\u7855 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
