\f1\b0 \cf2 "C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia kh\'f4ng?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i, "T\u7915  khi nghe tin L\'e2m Tr\u7909  ch\u7871 t t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c qu\u7927  d\u7883  r\u7845 t quen. Chuy\u7879 n x\u7843 y ra \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\'ednh l\'e0 nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t, thi th\u7875  \u7903  khu v\u7921 c xung quanh nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\u7841 i nh\u432  kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  'Ng\u259 n c\'e1ch', t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u cho r\u7857 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 c\'f2n s\u7889 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i v\u7899 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y chuy\u7879 n Tr\'ec Dung: "\u272 \u7871 n khi x\'e1c nh\u7853 n 'Tr\'ec Dung' m\'e0 t\'f4i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n ti\u7871 p x\'fac t\u7915  khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t, t\'f4i m\u7899 i th\u7921 c s\u7921  li\'ean h\u7879  t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y v\u7899 i th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia. L\'e2m Tr\u7909  c\u361 ng v\u7853 y, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i, L\'e2m Tr\u7909  m\'e0 Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n th\u7845 y l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra, m\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n khi h\u7891 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n b\u7903 i v\'ec nguy\'ean nh\'e2n n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 m\'e0 bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, ngay c\u7843  ma c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\'e0nh, m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra thi th\u7875  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i ra nh\uc0\u7919 ng \u273 i\u7873 u b\u7843 n th\'e2n quan s\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y ng\'e0y qua v\'e0 nh\u7919 ng ph\u7887 ng \u273 o\'e1n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y nghe xong gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean ng\u432 ng tr\u7885 ng: "C\u7853 u n\'f3i n\u417 i n\'e0y c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia, bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh m\u7897 t th\u7871  gi\u7899 i \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7843 o ngh\u7883 ch?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng sai, nh\uc0\u432 ng t\'f4i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i n\u417 i n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c \u273 \'f3 hay ch\u432 a. Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7871 n th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia n\u417 i \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng, t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng n\u417 i n\'e0y c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \u7905  h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \'edt nh\u7845 t nh\u432  Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, c\'e1c \u273 \u7841 i b\'e1 c\u7911 a c\u7853 u n\u7919 a, b\u7885 n h\u7885  h\u7859 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng b\u7883  h\u7841 i. Nh\u432 ng t\'ecnh h\'ecnh n\u417 i n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  ng\'e0y c\'e0ng nghi\'eam tr\u7885 ng, c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u thi\'ean s\u432  nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\'e0 v\u7851 n ph\'e2n kh\'f4ng bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 s\u7889 ng hay ch\u7871 t... Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y c\'f9ng l\'fac v\u7899 i ch\'fang ta, c\'f3 l\u7869  ch\'ed \'edt \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng, nh\u432 ng t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p M\'e3 Thi\'ean xem ra trong s\u7889  nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  gi\u7871 t r\u7891 i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u d\u7915 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "V\u7915 a r\u7891 i t\u7893  ph\u7909  t\'f4i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\'f3i mu\u7889 n g\u7863 p t\'f4i, t\'f4i l\u7841 i nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin b\'e1o \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i h\'f4n m\'ea, Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p x\u7871 p t\'e0i x\u7871  \u273 \u432 a t\'f4i \u273 i r\u7891 i, t\'f4i \u273 \u7883 nh g\u7863 p t\u7893  ph\u7909  xong s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c tr\u7903  v\u7873  ch\u259 m s\'f3c \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i. T\'ecnh h\'ecnh hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i r\u7845 t hung hi\u7875 m, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, t\'f4i ngh\u297  c\u7853 u v\'e0 Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t mau r\u7901 i \u273 i c\'f9ng t\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \u7875  t\'f4i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n \u273 \'e3." H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y kh\'f4ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ra quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh, \u7903  b\'ean kia \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i d\u7863 n d\'f2 m\u7897 t c\'e2u: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng c\u7849 n th\u7853 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i, xe \u273 \'fang l\'fac d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i \u7903  Tr\'ec gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean theo sau l\'e3o qu\uc0\u7843 n gia \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda ph\'f2ng Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  \u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'f2ng n\'e0y \uc0\u273 \'e3 c\'f3 l\u7883 ch s\u7917  h\u417 n ba tr\u259 m n\u259 m, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\'e2y d\u7921 ng b\u7857 ng g\u7895 , x\'e0 ngang r\u7845 t cao nh\u432 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec \'edt c\u7917 a s\u7893  n\'ean khi\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \'e2m u. Qu\u7843 n gia sau khi \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n th\'ec \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a r\u7901 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng c\'f3 m\uc0\u7897 t chi\u7871 c b\'e0n g\u7895 , m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gh\u7871  ph\'eda sau b\'e0n, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  v\u7889 n \u273 ang \u273 \u432 a l\u432 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u, nghe th\u7845 y \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh li\u7873 n quay l\u7841 i ch\'ednh di\u7879 n v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi nh\'ecn r\'f5 g\uc0\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \'f3, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 m\u7903  to hai m\u7855 t, h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng, t\u7915  trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng h\'f4 m\u7897 t c\'e2u r\u7845 t nh\u7887 , su\'fdt ch\'fat n\u7919 a \u273 \'e3 k\'eau ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang ng\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\u7893  ph\u7909  c\u7853 u r\u7845 t \'edt khi nh\'ecn th\u7845 y trong k\'fd \u7913 c m\'e0 ch\'ednh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u m\u7899 i g\u7863 p m\u7845 y ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\u361 ng v\u7915 a m\u7899 i b\u7845 t h\u7841 nh qua \u273 \u7901 i \'96 cha c\u7853 u Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t b\u7897  d\u7841 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n ti\u7873 u t\u7909 y v\'e0ng v\u7885 t l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, nh\'ecn qua v\u7851 n t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i c\'f3 s\u7913 c s\u7889 ng, ch\u7881  nh\u432  trong m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam gi\'e0 \u273 i m\u432 \u7901 i tu\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 nh gi\'e1c lui v\u7873  sau m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c, nh\'ecn ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885 : "\'d4ng l\'e0 ai?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i c\u7853 u, ch\u7881  nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7853 y m\'e0 l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  con t\u7899 i, h\u7891 n Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh r\'f5 r\'e0ng v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  Di\u7879 p gia, tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng l\'e2u m\u7899 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n tan bi\u7871 n. H\u7855 n bi\u7871 t r\'f5 chuy\u7879 n Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh m\'e0 v\u7851 n d\'e1m \u273 \u7875  con t\u7899 i g\u7863 p ta. Ta v\u7889 n c\'f2n chu\u7849 n b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng c\'e1ch kh\'e1c, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i xem ra kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n d\'f9ng n\u7919 a r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh l\'e0 t\'ean t\uc0\u7893  ph\u7909  Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u7913 ng t\u7887  h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 t\u7893  ph\u7909  Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh, c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n cha m\'ecnh. H\u7855 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t th\u7913  kho\'e1c da cha m\'ecnh. Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian suy ngh\u297  h\'e0m ngh\u297 a l\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i, ch\u7881  c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c h\u7887 i l\u7841 i: "\'d4ng l\'e0 ai?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  v\u7851 y tay v\u7899 i c\u7853 u: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, l\'e3o th\'e1i gia \u273 \'e2y. Khi c\'f2n b\'e9 con c\'f2n t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p ta m\'e0, m\u7899 i r\u7901 i nh\'e0 v\'e0i n\u259 m \u273 \'e3 qu\'ean r\u7891 i sao?"\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (th\'e1i gia: \'f4ng c\uc0\u7889 )
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e1i gia...th\'e1i gia c\uc0\u7911 a c\u7853 u, \'f4ng n\u7897 i c\u7911 a cha, r\'f5 r\'e0ng th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m m\u7865  c\'f2n mang thai c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 qua \u273 \u7901 i. C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p th\'e1i gia, nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t n\'f3i m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p h\u7855 n... Nh\u432  v\u7853 y \'fd h\u7855 n n\'f3i ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 "H\u7855 n" d\'f9ng th\'e2n ph\u7853 n kh\'e1c xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n .\cb1 \
\cb3 Li\'ean k\uc0\u7871 t v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i ban n\'e3y, trong ch\u7899 p nho\'e1ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\u297  r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u\'97\'97 ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  n\'f3i, khi c\'f2n nh\u7887  ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u cho r\u7857 ng l\'e0 \'f4ng n\u7897 i, k\u7923  th\u7853 t l\'e0 do v\u7883  "T\u7893  ph\u7909 " tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t n\'e0y kho\'e1c v\u7887  da Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh? H\'ecnh nh\u432  hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i h\u7855 n \u273 ang kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0m c\'e1ch n\'e0o \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i kho\'e1c da cha m\'ecnh? C\'f3 l\u7869  Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m bi\u7871 t ch\'fat chuy\u7879 n n\'ean m\u7899 i b\'ecnh th\u7843 n kh\'edch l\u7879  m\'ecnh t\u7921  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y t\'ecm hi\u7875 u t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u432  v\u7853 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ngh\uc0\u297  ti\u7871 p, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ph\'e2n t\'e2m truy x\'e9t nh\u7919 ng v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd ngh\u297 a g\'ec n\u7919 a. C\u7853 u l\u7845 y l\u7841 i b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, tho\'e1ng an t\'e2m, n\'f3i v\u7853 y ngh\u297 a l\'e0 Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m c\'f3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883 , s\u7869  kh\'f4ng sao c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c kia Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\'e0 do \'f4ng gi\u7843  m\u7841 o sao? \'d4ng c\u361 ng lu\'f4n bi\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n cha t\'f4i tr\'fang \u273 \u7897 c? Tr\'ec Dung l\'e0 do \'f4ng h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t t\'f4i c\u361 ng l\'e0 \'f4ng? L\u7847 n n\'e0y \'f4ng g\u7885 i t\'f4i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i t\'f4i ch\u7871 t sau \u273 \'f3 chi\u7871 m x\'e1c t\'f4i?" C\u7853 u nh\'ecn kh\'f4ng d\u7901 i m\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t t\u7921  x\u432 ng l\'e0 th\'e1i gia c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, n\'f3i th\u7859 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7841 m th\u7901 i b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y c\'f3 ph\u7843 i th\'e1i gia th\u7853 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u hay kh\'f4ng, n\u7871 u h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh, v\u7853 y vi\u7879 c h\u7855 n \'e2m th\u7847 m nh\'fang tay v\'e0o vi\u7879 c cha b\u7883  c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c thao t\'fang \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c .\cb1 \
\cb3 Cha l\'e0 con trai tr\uc0\u432 \u7903 ng Tr\'ec gia, \u7903  Tr\'ec gia c\'f3 l\u7921 c \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh, n\u7871 u nh\u432  \'f4ng t\u7881 nh t\'e1o, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng \u7903  cha m\'ecnh, s\u7869  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ng\u432 \u7901 i trong c\u417  th\u7875  Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 "Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh". N\u7871 u \'f4ng li\'ean h\u7907 p v\u7899 i c\'e1c t\u7897 c l\'e3o c\'f9ng v\u7841 ch tr\u7847 n, cho d\'f9 th\u7913  kia c\'f3 kho\'e1c da Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh th\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'e1ng c\u7921  n\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng n\u7871 u Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n b\u7903 i v\'ec b\u7883  h\u7841  c\u7893  m\'e0 th\u7847 n ch\'ed kh\'f4ng r\'f5, t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng s\u7869  kh\'e1c h\u7859 n. B\u7883  thao t\'fang, t\'e2m ch\'ed \u273 \u7841 i bi\u7871 n, \'f4ng s\u7869  r\u7845 t kh\'f3 ch\'fa \'fd t\u7899 i \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u7911 a cha m\'ecnh, k\u7867  th\u7871  th\'e2n kia s\u7869  kh\'f4ng lo l\u7855 ng vi\u7879 c b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n. Hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung kh\'f4ng c\'f3 d\'e3 t\'e2m, b\'e0 ta thao t\'fang Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n ch\u7881  v\'ec mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c "T\'ecnh y\'eau" b\u7879 nh tr\u7841 ng trong t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n sau khi b\u7883  h\u7841  c\u7893  s\u7869  ch\u7881  m\u7909  m\u7883  thi\'ean v\u7883  m\u7865  con b\u7885 n h\u7885  m\'e0 kh\'f4ng b\u7883  \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n l\'e0m ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec kh\'e1c, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng x\u7843 y ra phi\u7873 n ph\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Y\'ean t\'e2m, ta kh\'f4ng chi\uc0\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u417  th\u7875  ng\u432 \u417 i, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i cho ta bi\u7871 t c\'e1ch d\'f9ng qu\u7927  kh\'ed \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  k\'e9o d\'e0i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng, ta s\u7869  th\u7843  ng\u432 \u417 i \u273 i." K\u7867  kho\'e1c v\u7887  da Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n n\'f3i, sau \u273 \'f3 nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p th\u7915 a c\u417  gi\u7871 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7891 i kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  h\u7891 n ph\'e1ch c\u7853 u, ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t chung quy v\u7851 n d\u7877  kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  h\u417 n so v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng, d\'f9ng h\u7891 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n trao \u273 \u7893 i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\u7843  th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec t\u7889 t h\u417 n. Nh\u432 ng hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 thay \u273 \u7893 i ch\u7911  \'fd, \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  n\'e0y \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi xem ra quan tr\u7885 ng h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i h\u7855 n ngh\u297 , h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng g\'ec, nh\u432 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c khi t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1ch k\'e9o d\'e0i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng, h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng m\u7841 o hi\u7875 m \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng chi\uc0\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh? Qu\u7927  kh\'ed? Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'edu m\'e0y, n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y th\u7853 t s\u7921  tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p qu\u7927  kh\'ed gi\u7889 ng th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia \u432 ? T\u7841 i sao ng\u432 \u7901 i kia l\u7841 i n\'f3i kh\'f4ng chi\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7917  h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kia, h\u7855 n l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m n\u7919 a, ch\u7881  nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i d\u7921 a tr\'ean gh\u7871  d\u432 \u7905 ng th\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7907 t nh\u7899  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t s\u7921  ki\u7879 n. Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u b\u7889 n n\u259 m tu\u7893 i, m\u7897 t \'e1c qu\u7927  tr\u259 m n\u259 m b\u7883  t\u7893  ti\'ean Tr\'ec gia phong \u7845 n \u7903  c\u7845 m \u273 \u7883 a \u273 \'e3 tho\'e1t ra, ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n ph\'f2ng c\u7853 u \'fd \u273 \u7891  c\u432 \u7899 p \u273 o\u7841 t c\u417  th\u7875  c\'f2n nh\u7887  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u. \u272 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7899  l\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c h\u417 i l\u7841 nh ch\u7841 y d\u7885 c c\u7897 t s\u7889 ng chui v\'e0o trong n\'e3o, l\'fac \u7845 y kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c kh\'f3c l\u7899 n. Sau \u273 \'f3 h\u417 i l\u7841 nh l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t. Sau n\'e0y c\u7853 u l\u7899 n l\'ean m\u7897 t ch\'fat, nh\u7899  t\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y b\'e8n h\u7887 i m\u7865 , m\u7865  c\u7853 u n\'f3i khi ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec gia truy t\'ecm tung t\'edch \'e1c qu\u7927  kia \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n xem qua cho c\u7853 u, n\'f3i t\'e0 kh\'ed trong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u c\u7921 c th\u7883 nh, l\u7841 i ngang ng\u432 \u7907 c khinh ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i nh\u7845 t m\u7921 c h\'e0i h\'f2a t\u432 \u417 ng h\u7907 p v\u7899 i h\u7891 n c\u7853 u, \'e1c qu\u7927  kia v\u7915 a chui v\'e0o \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  t\'e0 kh\'ed trong c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7853 u c\u7855 n nu\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Cho n\'ean n\'f3i c\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  c\u361 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec ph\u7847 n t\'e0 kh\'ed n\'e0y n\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i kia m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng chi\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh? H\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 chi\u7871 m d\u7909 ng c\u417  th\u7875  t\u7893  ph\u7909  Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh r\u7891 i \u273 \u7871 n cha Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, n\u7871 u gi\u7843  thi\u7871 t h\u7855 n ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\'f9ng th\'e2n x\'e1c con ch\'e1u Tr\'ec gia, v\u7853 y chuy\u7879 n h\u7855 n \u7911 ng h\u7897  m\u7865  con Tr\'ec Dung v\'e0o c\u7917 a l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean\'97\'97 h\u7855 n l\u7841 i chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c cho m\'ecnh m\u7897 t v\u7853 t ch\u7913 a c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7917  d\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y vi\u7879 c l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c h\u7855 n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'fd gi\u7843 i, c\'f3 l\u7869  h\u7855 n d\u7921  c\u7843 m c\u417  th\u7875  t\u7893  ph\u7909  Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n c\u7921 c h\u7841 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  d\'f9ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, so v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n b\u7883  c\u7893  thao t\'fang nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m kh\'f4ng c\'f2n tr\u7867 , Tr\'ec Dung tu\u7893 i tr\u7867  kh\'ed th\u7883 nh \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean l\'e0 l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n t\u7889 t h\u417 n. Ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh x\'e1c kh\'f4, cho n\'ean h\u7855 n m\u7899 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng ch\u7885 n c\'e1ch \u7903  t\u7841 m trong th\'e2n x\'e1c Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n, ch\u7901  c\'e1i g\u7885 i l\'e0 "Bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p k\'e9o d\'e0i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng".\cb1 \
\cb3 "\'d4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t nh\u432 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y h\u7855 n, cho l\'e0 h\u7855 n c\'f2n s\u7889 ng? \'d4ng c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t n\u417 i n\'e0y c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t, bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh gi\u7889 ng Tr\'ec Dung, c\'f2n n\u417 i n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p tr\u7903  th\'e0nh m\u7897 t th\u7871  gi\u7899 i \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7843 o ngh\u7883 ch?" L\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 t t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n c\'f3 li\'ean quan t\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\'ec Vi\uc0\u7877 n S\u417 n" khi nghe \u273 \u7871 n "\'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7843 o ngh\u7883 ch" ch\u7907 t m\u7903  to m\u7855 t nh\'ecn c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7887 i: "V\'ec sao \'f4ng kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh Di\u7879 p gia c\'f3 c\'e1ch k\'e9o d\'e0i m\u7841 ng s\u7889 ng m\'e0 \'f4ng mu\u7889 n?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y ng\u432 \u7901 i kia tr\u7843  l\u7901 i c\u7853 u: "Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh h\u7891 n r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i x\'e1c nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y Di\u7879 p gia c\u361 ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch b\u7843 o v\u7879 , ch\u7913 ng t\u7887  qu\u7927  thu\u7853 t c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p gia th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng t\u7847 m th\u432 \u7901 ng. C\'f2n n\u7919 a, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'e1i d\u7841 ng kia \u273 \'e1ng l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m n\'ean ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i, nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\'e0 v\u7851 n c\'f2n n\u7917 a s\u7889 ng n\u7917 a ch\u7871 t, h\u417 n n\u7919 a qu\u7927  kh\'ed tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'e1c qu\u7927  kh\'ed v\'e2y quanh n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y, \u273 \u7873 u c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng d\'e0y, c\'e1ch gi\u7843 i th\'edch duy nh\u7845 t ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 d\'f9ng qu\u7927  kh\'ed thi\'ean \u273 \u7883 a \u273 \u7875  k\'e9o d\'e0i m\u7841 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7917 a b\u7883  g\'f5 nh\u7865  ba c\'e1i, b\'ean ngo\'e0i vang l\'ean m\u7897 t gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i l\'e0nh l\u7841 nh l\u7841 i d\u7883 u d\'e0ng: "A Di\'ean, xe \u273 ang \u273 \u7907 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i \u273 \u432 a em tr\u7903  v\u7873  th\u259 m ngo\u7841 i, em mau ra \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn tho\'e1ng qua v\uc0\u7873  ph\'eda sau, l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7917 a \u273 \u7849 y nh\u7865  m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 \'e3 m\u7903 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7913 ng ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\u7853 u li\u7873 n c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, s\u7901  l\'ean m\u7863 t c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t h\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "... V\uc0\u7851 n ch\u432 a." Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7911  r\u361  h\u7841  m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec. L\'e1t n\u7919 a \u273 \u7875  ta thay em n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i v\u7883  ti\'ean sinh n\'e0y, em mau \u273 i \u273 i, \u273 \u7907 i ca ca \u273 i t\'ecm em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean mu\uc0\u7889 n h\u7887 i h\u7855 n v\u7873  Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh v\'e0 chuy\u7879 n qu\u7927  kh\'ed k\'e9o d\'e0i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng; mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m bi\u7871 t t\u7893  ph\u7909  th\u7853 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, v\u7883  t\u7893  ph\u7909  kia l\'e0 do m\u7897 t th\u7913  kh\'f4ng r\'f5 kho\'e1c da ng\u432 \u7901 i hay kh\'f4ng; mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i h\u7855 n c\'f3 \u273 \u7889 i s\'e1ch g\'ec v\u7899 i t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7843 o ngh\u7883 ch \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y hay kh\'f4ng... Nh\u432 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t xem ra kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m t\u7889 t, trong ph\'f2ng c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7913  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 g\'ec kia \u273 ang ch\u7901 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ch\u7881  kh\u7869  ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, h\'f4n l\'ean b\'ean tai Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t c\'e1i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, \u273 \u7915 ng l\'e0m c\u417  th\u7875  cha em b\u7883  h\u432  h\u7841 i, gi\'fap \'f4ng \u7845 y \u273 em th\'e2n x\'e1c c\u361 ng an t\'e1ng t\u7889 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\'f9ng \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t t\u7889 i \u273 en nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, s\u7901  l\'ean m\'f4i c\u7853 u: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t k\u7875  \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec, Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng thua.\cb1 \
