\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i ra thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i d\u7883  th\u432 \u7901 ng, th\u7913  kia kh\'f4ng t\u7887  b\u7845 t k\u7923  th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  g\'ec. Thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c c\u7853 u t\u7921  l\u7849 m b\u7849 m trong l\'f2ng, nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m l\'ean c\u7845 p ba c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 xem kh\'f4ng \'edt phim \u273 \u7885 c kh\'f4ng \'edt truy\u7879 n, k\u7883 ch b\u7843 n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i th\u7871  n\'e0y. Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o sau khi \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t nh\'e2n v\u7853 t ph\u7843 n di\u7879 n c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  r\u7901 i \u273 i d\u7877  d\'e0ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y, tr\u7915  khi \u273 \'f3 v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i k\u7867  \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7847 u th\u7853 t s\u7921 , ph\'eda sau v\u7851 n c\'f2n k\u7867  l\u7907 i h\u7841 i h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Song c\uc0\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 b\u7853 n t\'e2m, d\'f9 sao \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 hi\u7879 n th\u7921 c, s\u7869  c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7845 t l\u7907 i h\u7841 i, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe Di\uc0\u7879 p gia qu\u7843  nhi\'ean \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7907 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i. Ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  l\'e1i xe, ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i ph\'eda sau Th\u432 \u7907 ng c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\'e0 H\u7913 a H\'e2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a H\'e2n ng\u7891 i trong xe, \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n n\'f3i: "Anh t\'f4i b\u7843 o t\'f4i \u273 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, \u273 ang mu\u7889 n m\u7903  c\u7917 a l\'ean xe, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7841 y \u273 u\u7893 i t\u7899 i, trong mi\u7879 ng h\'f4: "\u272 \u7841 i thi\u7871 u gia, ch\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat!"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, L\'fd M\u7841 o \'f4m m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p nh\u7887  m\'e0u \u273 en \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n c\u7853 u: "\u272 \u7841 i thi\u7871 u gia, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 th\u7913  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n l\'fac thu x\u7871 p l\u7841 i di v\u7853 t c\u7911 a Nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u gia, ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t l\'e1 th\u432 , n\'f3i l\'e0 l\u432 u l\u7841 i cho ng\'e0i."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i l\'e0 th\uc0\u432 , k\u7923  th\u7853 t ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7901  gi\u7845 y nh\u7887 , tr\'ean gi\u7845 y vi\u7871 t mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p n\'e0y cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean do d\uc0\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n c\u7843 m \u417 n r\u7891 i nh\u7853 n l\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7901 i n\'e0y Tr\'ec Dung ch\u7881  c\'f3 hai l\u7847 n duy nh\u7845 t th\u7875  hi\u7879 n \'fd t\u7889 t v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, l\'e0 sau khi ch\u7871 t v\u7851 n c\'f2n c\u7843 nh b\'e1o c\u7853 u mau r\u7901 i \u273 i v\'e0 nh\u7855 c c\u7853 u nh\u7901  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ti\u7877 n \u273 \u432 a Tr\'ec Vi\u7877 n S\u417 n. Cho n\'ean nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c trong chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 g\'ec, l\'e0 thi\u7879 n \'fd l\u432 u l\u7841 i manh m\u7889 i cho c\u7853 u hay l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i. Cho d\'f9 kh\'f4ng h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec n\u7871 u l\'e0 m\u7897 t h\u7897 p s\'e2u gi\u7889 ng chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p s\u7855 t m\'e0 m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i L\'fd M\u7841 o ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, ph\u7887 ng ch\u7915 ng c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \'f4m chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p ng\u7891 i v\'e0o trong xe, H\u7913 a H\'e2n t\'f2 m\'f2 l\u7841 i g\u7847 n: "\u272 \u7875  l\u7841 i g\'ec cho c\u7853 u th\u7871 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 a chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p cho c\'f4 xem, nh\u7855 c nh\u7903 : "C\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a H\'e2n mu\u7889 n th\u7917  m\u7903  ra l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng m\u7903  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 \'e0nh tr\u7843  l\u7841 i cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng v\u7897 i m\u7903  h\u7897 p, quay sang H\u7913 a H\'e2n h\u7887 i: "H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \'e2u? Sao c\u7853 u ta kh\'f4ng \u273 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u m\'e0 l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u \u273 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a H\'e2n \u273 \'e1p: "Nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n c\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7899 i anh \u7845 y t\'f4i \u273 \u7873 u bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i. Anh \u7845 y lo cho cha m\u7865 , b\u7843 o l\'e0 mu\u7889 n \u273 i gi\u7843 i th\'edch v\u7899 i h\u7885  r\u7891 i d\u7851 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i c\'f9ng, b\u7843 o t\'f4i \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c v\u7899 i c\u7853 u, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  s\u7861 n m\u7885 i th\u7913  ch\u7901  anh \u7845 y \u273 \u432 a cha m\u7865  r\u7901 i H\u7913 a gia \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  L r\u7891 i s\u7889 ng \u7903  \u273 \'f3."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 N\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y n\'e9t m\u7863 t c\'f4 hi\u7879 n l\'ean ch\'fat lo s\u7847 u: "T\'f4i c\u361 ng lo cho anh v\u7899 i cha m\u7865 . M\u7865  c\'f2n d\u7877  n\'f3i, cha th\'ec kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c s\u7869  tin anh t\'f4i ngay, cho d\'f9 tin, \'f4ng \u7845 y kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng y\'ean l\'f2ng b\'e1c c\u7843  v\'e0 \'f4ng n\u7897 i, b\'e1c c\u7843  v\'e0 l\u7841 i \'f4ng n\u7897 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  b\u7887  l\u7841 i to\'e0n b\u7897  H\u7913 a gia... B\u7903 i v\u7853 y s\u7869  phi\u7873 n to\'e1i h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng an \u7911 i c\'f4: "V\u7851 n c\'f2n Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca m\'e0, h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng sao \u273 \'e2u."\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u7853 u c\u361 ng r\u7845 t lo l\u7855 ng, tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t t\'ecnh h\'ecnh n\u417 i n\'e0y xem ra nghi\'eam tr\u7885 ng h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u so v\u7899 i th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c. Trong th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia c\'f9ng l\u7855 m ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'f2n n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y l\u7841 i t\u7909  h\u7897 i g\u7847 n nh\u432  t\u7845 t c\u7843  c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432  c\'f3 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c, nh\u432 ng nhi\u7873 u thi\'ean s\u432  nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\'e0 v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra d\u7883  tr\u7841 ng. \u272 \'e1ng s\u7907  h\u417 n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng khi g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n ma qu\'e1i kh\'f4ng gi\u7843 i th\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7869  \u273 i t\'ecm thi\'ean s\u432  nh\u7901  gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , nh\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  b\u7903 i v\'ec l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u thi\'ean s\u432  gi\u7887 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 r\u417 i v\'e0o c\u7909 c, b\u7885 n c\u7853 u m\u7863 c d\'f9 ch\u7841 y ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432 ng sau n\'e0y n\u7871 u l\u7841 i g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n th\'ec bi\u7871 t \u273 i t\'ecm ai xin gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  \u273 \'e2y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ngh\uc0\u297  ti\u7871 p, *c\'f9ng th\'ec gi\u7919  m\'ecnh trong s\u7841 ch, \u273 \u7841 t th\'ec c\u7913 u gi\'fap thi\'ean h\u7841 , c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng qu\u7843 n qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u. Tr\'ec gia \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  g\u7885 i l\'e0 "Ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n", \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i c\u7853 u m\'e0 n\'f3i, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca v\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y b\'ecnh an tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ki\u7871 p n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 t\u7889 t l\u7855 m r\u7891 i, nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n c\'f2n l\u7841 i c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m mong c\u7847 u xa v\u7901 i.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (* \uc0\u273 \u7841 i \'fd l\'e0 r\u417 i v\'e0o c\u7843 nh ngh\'e8o kh\'f3 th\'ec c\u7889  g\u7855 ng tu d\u432 \u7905 ng gi\u7919  l\'f2ng trong s\u7841 ch, khi th\'e0nh c\'f4ng r\u7891 i th\'ec gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c)
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7875  d\u7901 i l\u7921 c ch\'fa \'fd, c\u7853 u n\'e2ng chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p Tr\'ec Dung \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i cho m\'ecnh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\'ecm hi\u7875 u. Chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p kh\'f4ng kh\'f3a, nh\u432 ng ph\u7847 n gi\u7919 a n\u7855 p v\'e0 th\'e2n h\u7897 p l\u7841 i \u273 \'ednh ti\'eau b\u7843 n m\u7897 t lo\'e0i c\'f4n tr\'f9ng nh\'ecn gi\u7889 ng ve s\u7847 u, g\u7855 n ch\u7863 t chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7917  m\u7903  ra, con ve s\u7847 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c r\u7899 t xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i n\u7855 p h\u7897 p c\u361 ng b\u7853 t l\'ean. B\'ean trong \u273 \u7921 ng m\u7897 t quy\u7875 n s\'e1ch nh\u7887  v\'e0 m\u7897 t t\u7901  gi\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7845 p l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u7903  quy\u7875 n s\'e1ch ra tr\u432 \u7899 c, b\'ean trong v\u7869  c\'e1c lo\u7841 i c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c, c\'f2n c\'f3 v\u259 n t\u7921 , nh\'ecn qua ch\'ednh l\'e0 ghi ch\'e9p v\u7873  c\u7893  thu\u7853 t Qu\u7923 nh Ch\'e2u. V\'ec chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a cha, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p n\'e0y ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ch\'e1n gh\'e9t, kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n hi\u7875 u r\'f5 th\'eam, xem s\u417  qua r\u7891 i kh\'e9p l\u7841 i c\u7845 t v\'e0o h\u7897 p, l\u7845 y t\u7901  gi\u7845 y kia ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7897 i dung vi\u7871 t tr\'ean gi\u7845 y d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  l\'e0 nh\u7853 t k\'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7889 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\u7887 ng \u273 o\'e1n, n\u7897 i dung ghi ch\'e9p \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  h\u417 n hai m\u432 \u417 i ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Dung \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n c\u7893  tr\'f9ng c\u7911 a g\'e3 ch\u7871 t b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 g\'e3 th\'f4ng qua d\u7851 n d\u7855 t c\u7893  thu\u7853 t, "T\'ecm th\u7845 y" thi th\u7875  ch\'ednh m\'ecnh d\u432 \u7899 i g\u7847 m gi\u432 \u7901 ng, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra s\u7921  th\u7853 t m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t. Nh\u432 ng c\'f9ng l\'fac \u273 \'f3 g\'e3 c\'f2n ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n qu\u7927  d\u7883  kh\'e1c, trong thi th\u7875  c\u7911 a g\'e3 \u7849 n gi\u7845 u nh\u7919 ng m\u7843 nh h\u7891 n kh\'f4ng thu\u7897 c v\u7873  g\'e3, nh\u7919 ng m\u7843 nh h\u7891 n n\'e0y dung h\u7907 p r\u7845 t t\u7889 t v\u7899 i c\u417  th\u7875  g\'e3, \'edt nh\u7845 t \u273 \'e3 h\u417 n m\u432 \u7901 i n\u259 m. C\u361 ng b\u7903 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 thi th\u7875  c\u7911 a g\'e3 m\u7863 c d\'f9 l\'e0 tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i "\u272 \'e3 ch\u7871 t" nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\'f2n duy tr\'ec m\u7897 t d\'f2ng sinh kh\'ed mong manh, t\'f9y th\u7901 i c\'f3 th\u7875  "S\u7889 ng l\u7841 i".\cb1 \
\cb3 Xu\uc0\u7845 t th\'e2n t\u7915  thi\'ean s\u432  th\u7871  gia, r\u7845 t nhanh g\'e3 hi\u7875 u r\u7857 ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7911  m\u432 u mu\u7889 n \u273 o\u7841 t c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh. Nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i g\'e3 c\u361 ng \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, n\u7871 u c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 u\u7893 i nh\u7919 ng m\u7843 nh h\u7891 n kia \u273 i, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n tr\u7903  l\u7841 i trong c\u417  th\u7875 , nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n kh\u7843  n\u259 ng "s\u7889 ng l\u7841 i" n\'e0o \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y, g\'e3 d\u7851 n nh\u7919 ng c\u7893  tr\'f9ng c\'f2n s\u7889 ng v\'e0o trong ng\u432 \u7901 i, d\'f9ng h\u7891 n m\'ecnh d\u7851 n d\u7855 t ch\'fang, n\u7871 u nh\u432  g\'e3 th\'e0nh c\'f4ng xu\u7845 t ph\u7847 n h\u7891 n c\u7911 a "K\u7867  kia" \u273 i, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  c\'f3 th\u7875  xua ch\'fang ra, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u th\u7845 t b\u7841 i s\u7869  tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  h\u7891 n phi ph\'e1ch t\'e1n, c\u7893  tr\'f9ng m\u7845 t \u273 i d\u7851 n d\u7855 t s\u7869  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c h\'fat kh\'f4 huy\u7871 t nh\u7909 c v\'e0 sinh kh\'ed c\'f2n s\'f3t l\u7841 i trong ng\u432 \u7901 i g\'e3. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c n\u7893  tung m\'e0 ch\u7871 t, c\u417  th\u7875  c\u7911 a g\'e3 c\u361 ng s\u7869  ho\'e0n to\'e0n bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh m\u7897 t b\u7897  th\'e2y kh\'f4.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 o\u7841 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ghi ch\'e9p g\'ec th\'eam, Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\'ednh to\'e1n th\u7901 i gian, khi \u273 \'f3 m\'ecnh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  l\u7841 i Tr\'ec gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7899  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c L\'fd M\u7841 o t\u7915 ng nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n, tr\u432 \u7899 c khi Tr\'ec Dung "M\u7845 t t\'edch", l\u7847 n cu\u7889 i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y g\'e3 l\'e0 tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  b\u7871  quan. C\u7853 u suy \u273 o\'e1n Tr\'ec Dung b\u7857 ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra linh h\u7891 n \u7849 n n\'e1u trong c\u417  th\u7875  g\'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 o\u7841 t x\'e1 \u273 ang s\u7889 ng nh\u7901  trong c\u417  th\u7875  Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917 , cho n\'ean \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 sau khi cha qua \u273 \u7901 i g\'e3 \u273 \'e3 \u273 i t\'ecm th\u7913  kia, \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 o\u7841 t l\u7841 i c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh. Nh\u432 ng nh\'ecn k\u7871 t qu\u7843 , xem ra g\'e3 \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 t b\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7845 t k\u7929  t\u7901  gi\u7845 y v\'e0 cu\u7889 n s\'e1ch nh\u7887 , c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 ch\'fat th\u7893 n th\u7913 c, m\u7865  Tr\'ec Dung h\u7841 i c\u7853 u c\u7843  nh\'e0 ly t\'e1n, nh\u432 ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng m\u7865  con b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7871 t kh\'f4ng t\u7917  t\u7871 , th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 m\u7897 t cu\u7897 c giao d\u7883 ch h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng l\u7907 i m\'ecnh. M\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung c\'f3 l\u7869  v\u7851 n c\'f2n nh\u7899  m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7875 m t\'ecnh ngh\u297 a anh em c\'f9ng cha kh\'e1c m\u7865 , cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng v\u7851 n \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i manh m\u7889 i cho c\u7853 u, n\u7871 u c\u7853 u s\u7899 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c chi\u7871 c h\u7897 p nh\u7887  n\'e0y th\'ec \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  v\u7873  "T\u7893  ph\u7909  Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh" s\u7899 m h\u417 n. Song b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd ngh\u297 a g\'ec n\u7919 a, Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca \u273 \'e3 thu x\u7871 p m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n \u7893 n th\u7887 a, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u n\u7857 m trong tay h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xe ch\uc0\u7841 y th\u7859 ng m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i ba nh\'e0 Tr\'ec H\u7913 a Di\u7879 p \u7849 n th\u7871 , xe c\u7897  tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng d\u7847 n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n. H\u7913 a H\'e2n v\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a s\u7893  \u273 \u7871 n xu\u7845 t th\u7847 n, c\u7843  hai \u273 \u7873 u lo l\u7855 ng, ai c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e2m t\u432  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau, c\u7843  m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c \u273 \u7871 n \u273 i\u7875 m d\u7915 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi \uc0\u273 \u432 a H\u7913 a H\'e2n v\u7873  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  L, t\'e0i x\u7871  \u273 \u432 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7871 n b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n ch\u7895  \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R xong ch\'e0o c\u7853 u r\u7891 i quay v\u7873  nh\u7853 n l\u7879 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tr\'ec ho\'e3n, v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'f2ng b\u7879 nh \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i n\u7857 m, b\u7903 i v\'ec c\'f3 \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean c\'f9ng ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u259 m s\'f3c lu\'f4n gi\'fap tr\'f4ng nom, t\'ecnh h\'ecnh \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879  l\u7855 m, c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng s\u7841 ch s\u7869 , ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u hai ng\'e0y nay v\u7851 n ch\u432 a t\u7881 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'e1m \u417 n T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u7903  b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n c\u7843  ng\'e0y \u273 \'eam ch\u259 m s\'f3c \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i. M\u7863 c d\'f9 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'fap vi\u7879 c c\'f9ng v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ho\'e0n to\'e0n bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng, v\'e0i ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c v\u7915 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nu\'f4i cho b\'e9o h\u417 n ch\'fat l\u7841 i nhanh ch\'f3ng g\u7847 y \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t tu\u7847 n tr\'f4i qua r\u7845 t nhanh, b\'e1c s\u297  n\'f3i th\u7853 t s\u7921  n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng t\u7881 nh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o, \u273 \u432 a v\u7873  nh\'e0 ch\u259 m s\'f3c chu \u273 \'e1o l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, khi n\'e0o c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i th\'ec kh\'f4ng th\u7875  bi\u7871 t, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\u7857 m vi\u7879 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i \u273 \u7875  quan s\'e1t th\'eam hai ng\'e0y xem sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m nay ch\uc0\u7841 ng v\u7841 ng t\u7889 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a mu\u7889 n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i mua c\u417 m ch\u7907 t th\u7845 y T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u7847 m c\u7863 p l\u7891 ng \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , h\'f4m nay Quy\'ean Quy\'ean l\'e0m th\u7883 t kho t\'e0u, c\u7853 u \u259 n m\u7897 t \'edt \u273 i. G\u7855 ng g\u432 \u7907 ng m\u7895 i ng\'e0y nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng hay, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng th\'ec t\u259 ng ti\u7873 n t\u259 ng th\u7901 i gian l\'e0m cho ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\'fap vi\u7879 c, c\u7853 u ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i cho kh\u7887 e \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893 : "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng y\'ean t\'e2m, gi\u7901  t\'f4i ch\u7881  c\'f2n \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean n\'f3i g\'ec, v\u7895  vai c\u7853 u: "Ng\'e0y mai t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881 , t\u7915  t\u7889 i nay \u273 \u7871 n t\u7889 i mai t\'f4i s\u7869  ch\u259 m ngo\u7841 i, c\u7853 u v\u7873  t\u7855 m r\u7917 a ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i \u273 i, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\u7853 u \u7889 m th\'ec ai ch\u259 m ngo\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y. T\'f4i tr\'f4ng ngo\u7841 i th\'ec c\u7853 u y\'ean t\'e2m r\u7891 i ch\u7913 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\uc0\u7915  ch\u7889 i n\u7919 a, trong l\'f2ng ngh\u297  s\'e1ng mai s\u7869  t\u7899 i thay T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m. C\u7843  ng\'e0y h\'f4m nay c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  r\u7845 t m\u7879 t r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng x\u7889 c n\u7893 i tinh th\u7847 n n\u7919 a, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m n\'f3i c\'f3 l\'fd, c\u7853 u qu\u7843  th\u7921 c c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7873  nh\'e0 t\u7855 m r\u7917 a xong lau qua ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i m\u7863 c \'e1o cho\'e0ng t\u7855 m \u273 i ra, chui th\u7859 ng v\'e0o ch\u259 n, n\u7857 m l\'ean g\u7889 i nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ng\u7911 . C\u7853 u qu\'e1 m\u7879 t, ngay c\u7843  \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7845 c n\u7893 i, th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i ng\u7911  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'fac n\uc0\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7915 ng lu\u7891 ng h\u417 i l\u7841 nh, qu\u7845 n k\'edn ch\u259 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, qua m\u7897 t l\'fac to\'e0n th\'e2n l\u7841 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u nhanh ch\'f3ng n\'f3ng l\'ean, t\u7887 a nhi\u7879 t khi\u7871 n c\u7853 u v\'f4 c\'f9ng kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u. L\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u m\u417  m\u417  h\u7891  h\u7891  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 m\u7897 t v\'f2ng \'f4m quen thu\u7897 c, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m m\'e0 l\u259 n t\u7899 i, chen v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 t nh\u7887  trong ng\u7921 c kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng cu\u7897 n tr\'f2n chui v\'e0o c\u7885  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh, \'e1o t\u7855 m \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m tu\u7897 t m\u7845 t, hai tay \'f4m ch\u7863 t m\'ecnh, trong mi\u7879 ng c\'f2n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng l\u7849 m b\u7849 m "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca" "Ca kh\'f4ng y\'eau kh\'f4ng y\'eau em " "\u7902  b\'ean em \u273 i" "Em th\'edch ca ca nh\u7845 t" "Y\'eau y\'eau em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng ", l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t. Th\u7871  nh\u432 ng hai m\u7855 t c\u7853 u l\u7841 i nh\u7855 m ch\u7863 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng n\'f3ng nh\u432  b\u7883  s\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh t\u7899 i th\u7853 t \u273 \'fang l\'fac, ch\u7881  h\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7911  \u7845 n c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c \u259 n \u273 \u7871 n x\u432 \u417 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n. L\'fd tr\'ed l\u7841 i n\'f3i ph\u7843 i nh\u7851 n n\u7841 i ki\u7873 m ch\u7871 , A Di\'ean th\u7871  n\'e0y r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 sinh b\u7879 nh b\u7883  s\u7889 t, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\'e0y v\'f2, ph\u7843 i \'f4m trong l\'f2ng c\u7849 n th\u7853 n ch\u259 m m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  h\'f4n v\'e0nh tai Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "B\u7843 o b\u7889 i, kh\'f4ng l\'e0m, em b\u7883  b\u7879 nh r\u7891 i. N\'f3i cho ca ca, thu\u7889 c \u273 \u7875  \u7903  \u273 \'e2u, ta \u273 i l\u7845 y thu\u7889 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i m\u7863 c k\u7879  h\u7855 n, ch\u7881  \'f4m h\u7855 n c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng r\u7847 m r\'ec c\u7885  t\u7899 i c\u7885  lui.\cb1 \
