\f1\b0 \cf2 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o, \u273 \'e0nh m\u7903  di \u273 \u7897 ng t\u7843 i \u7913 ng d\u7909 ng giao thu\u7889 c to\'e0n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  trong 24h, mua lo\u7841 i thu\u7889 c h\u7841  s\u7889 t th\u432 \u7901 ng d\'f9ng. V\u7915 a ch\u7901  thu\u7889 c giao \u273 \u7871 n v\u7915 a \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e1ch m\u7897 t l\u7899 p ch\u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\'f3ng, l\u7841 i b\u7883  h\u7855 n qu\u7845 n trong ch\u259 n kh\'f4ng h\u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0o, kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng kh\'f3c nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m c\u7853 u th\u7847 m th\'ec "Em kh\'f3c \u273 i, kh\'f3c r\u7891 i c\'f3 th\u7845 y d\u7877  ch\u7883 u h\u417 n kh\'f4ng? L\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 ca ca b\u7903 i v\'ec em kh\'f3c m\'e0 m\u7873 m l\'f2ng bu\'f4ng tha, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i em c\'f2n kh\'f3c l\u7899 n h\u417 n sao." Ngo\'e0i mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i l\u7901 i \'e1m mu\u7897 i, th\u7921 c t\'e2m l\u7841 i \u273 au l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng th\'f4i, h\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  b\u7879 nh thay c\u7853 u, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 D\uc0\u7851 u c\'f3 t\u7845 t c\u7843  s\u7913 c m\u7841 nh, h\u7855 n v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  qu\u7843 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c sinh l\'e3o b\u7879 nh t\u7917  c\u7911 a nh\'e2n th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 N\uc0\u7917 a gi\u7901  sau thu\u7889 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7871 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7895  Tr\'ec Di\'ean cu\u7889 n c\u7853 u th\'e0nh c\'e1i b\'e1nh \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 i m\u7903  c\u7917 a l\u7845 y thu\u7889 c, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i l\u7845 y n\u432 \u7899 c mang thu\u7889 c \u273 \u7871 n cho c\u7853 u u\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong l\'fac n\uc0\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea kh\'f4ng t\'ecm th\u7845 y h\u7855 n, g\u7845 p \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c l\u259 n l\u7897 n lung tung, ch\u7881  ch\u7889 c l\'e1t ch\u259 n \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  tung ra h\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n ng\u7911 , \u273 \u7863 t thu\u7889 c v\u7899 i n\u432 \u7899 c l\'ean t\u7911  \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng cu\u7897 n c\u7853 u l\u7841 i \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t nh\u432 ng kh\'f3e m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 h\u417 i \'e1nh n\u432 \u7899 c, \u273 \u432 a ng\'f3n tay s\u7901  th\u7917 , \u432 \u7899 t nh\u7865 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Th\uc0\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f3c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi "H\u7915 m" r\u7891 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, n\u7897 i t\'e2m m\u7873 m ra, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e2m m\u7897 t c\'e1i tim c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  tho\'e1t n\u432 \u7899 c, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o v\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Hu\u7889 ng chi hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang s\u7889 t m\'ea man, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng th\'e8m n\'f3i l\'fd, ch\u7881  m\u7873 m nh\u361 n d\'ednh l\u7845 y h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7895  c\u7853 u nh\u432  d\u7895  con n\'edt: "Ca ca \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, ca ca v\u7915 a \u273 i l\u7845 y thu\u7889 c cho A Di\'ean. H\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 H\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i xong h\'f4n hai m\'e1 Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean li\u7873 n ngoan ngo\'e3n trong ch\u7889 c l\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, th\u7915 a c\u417  d\u7895  d\'e0nh c\u7853 u: "Ngoan, b\u7843 o b\u7889 i u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c \u273 i, u\u7889 ng xong ca ca l\u7841 i th\u432 \u417 ng em."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean u\uc0\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c r\u7845 t ph\u7889 i h\u7907 p, kh\'f4ng nh\'e1o, u\u7889 ng xong c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng g\'e2y chuy\u7879 n, c\'e1ch m\u7897 t l\u7899 p ch\u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m trong ng\u7921 c y\'ean l\u7863 ng m\'e0 ng\u7911 . Nh\u432 ng m\u7897 t l\'e1t sau c\u7853 u l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng r\u7847 m r\'ec, chui v\'e0o trong l\'f2ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi du\u7895 i tay v\'e0o ch\u259 n s\u7901  th\u7917 , ch\u259 n h\u417 i \u7849 m, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\u7891  h\'f4i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Tay h\uc0\u7855 n l\u7841 nh, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p ch\u7841 m v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u432 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 \u432 \u7899 t \u273 \u7851 m, ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i. V\'ec v\u7853 y l\u7841 i t\'ecm m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c ch\u259 n kh\'e1c, nhanh ch\'f3ng qu\u7845 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o ch\u259 n m\u7899 i kh\'f4 r\'e1o, g\u7841 t ch\u259 n c\u361  qua b\'ean kia gi\u432 \u7901 ng, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7875  Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  d\'ednh gi\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \uc0\u272 \u7893 i ch\u259 n xong Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7899 t kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u h\u417 n, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u \u273 ang b\u7879 nh, v\u7851 n ch\u432 a h\u7841  s\u7889 t, d\'f9 th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, ch\'f4n trong ng\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng r\u7847 m r\'ec, d\u7909 i m\u7863 t v\'e0o ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i \'f4m c\u7853 u c\'e1ch m\u7897 t l\u7899 p ch\u259 n nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c, tay v\u7895  nh\'e8 nh\u7865 . Trong l\'f2ng ngh\u297  nh\'e0 n\'e0o \u273 \u7909 ng tr\'fang ti\u7875 u b\u7843 o b\u7889 i n\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u h\u7871 t c\'e1ch, ai b\u7843 o A Di\'ean l\u7841 i r\u417 i v\'e0o tay m\'ecnh ch\u7913 , nh\u432 ng\'a0 n\u7871 u A Di\'ean r\u417 i v\'e0o tay ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, c\'f3 l\u7869  h\u7855 n s\u7869  n\u7893 i \u273 i\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Qua m\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \'eam nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\'f4m sau Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  m\u7899 i t\u7881 nh, l\'fac ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh n\u7857 m trong ng\u7921 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7853 p t\u7913 c l\u7855 p b\u7855 p, nh\'ecn b\u7889 n ph\'eda xung quanh, \u273 \'e2y l\u7841 i \u273 \'fang l\'e0 nh\'e0 m\'ecnh v\u7899 i ngo\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 C\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 h\u7841  s\u7889 t nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n y\u7871 u, c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7911 n r\u7911 n v\'f4 l\u7921 c, \u273 \u432 a tay ch\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, sao ca ca l\u7841 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y? Ca ca \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y l\'fac n\'e0o? V\'e0o b\u7857 ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 C\uc0\u7853 u v\u7915 a v\u7845 t v\u7843  \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\u7841 i \u7845 n c\u7853 u v\u7873  nh\'e9t v\'e0o ch\u259 n: "H\'f4m qua l\'e0m vi\u7879 c xong mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7871 n h\u417 i mu\u7897 n, v\u7889 n \u273 \u7883 nh xem em \u273 \'e3 ng\u7911  ch\u432 a, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n em ngay c\u7843  c\u7917 a c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng kh\'f3a n\'ean c\u7913  v\u7853 y \u273 i v\'e0o. May m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'e0o l\'e0 ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t "V\'e2ng" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng. C\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899  r\'f5 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 kh\'f3a hay ch\u432 a, theo l\'fd m\'e0 n\'f3i c\u7853 u c\'f3 th\'f3i quen kh\'f3a c\u7917 a, nh\u432 ng nghe v\u7853 y c\u361 ng h\u417 i ch\u7897 t d\u7841 , kh\'f4ng ch\'fat nghi ng\u7901  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e1p: "Ch\u7855 c h\'f4m qua v\u7873  xong m\u7879 t qu\'e1 n\'ean em qu\'ean m\u7845 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 N\'f3i xong c\uc0\u7853 u \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7899  t\u7899 i th\u7913  \u7903  Tr\'ec gia, l\u7841 i v\u7897 i v\'e3 chui ra \'f4m c\'e1nh tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, th\u7913  \u7903  Tr\'ec gia kia r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 g\'ec? Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng h\u7855 n th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, l\u7841 i nh\'e9t c\u7853 u v\'e0o ch\u259 n r\u7891 i m\u7899 i ch\u7853 m r\'e3i n\'f3i: "Vi\u7879 c n\'e0y n\'f3i ra r\u7845 t d\'e0i. \u272 \u7847 u ti\'ean, h\u417 n hai m\u432 \u417 i n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c khi em c\'f2n ch\u432 a ra \u273 \u7901 i, c\'f3 m\u7897 t du h\u7891 n d\'f9ng b\'ed thu\u7853 t c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  t\'ecm \u273 \u7871 n cha ta c\u7847 u c\u7913 u, ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\u7893  ph\u7909  Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh c\u7911 a em, khi \u273 \'f3 th\'e2n x\'e1c \'f4ng \u7845 y \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  kh\'e1c chi\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, xin gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  c\u361 ng v\'f4 \'edch. Tr\'ec gia c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p gia d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7851 n \'e2m th\u7847 m c\'f3 m\u7845 y th\u7913  kh\'f4ng s\u7841 ch, cha ta nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean gi\'fap \'f4ng \u7845 y th\u7871  n\'e0o, b\'e8n d\'f9ng b\'ed thu\u7853 t gia truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7875  \'f4ng \u7845 y s\u7889 ng nh\u7901  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t c\u7895  ho\u7841 t thi 
\f2\i (*x\'e1c s\uc0\u7889 ng)
\f1\i0 , gi\uc0\u7845 u b\'ean trong Di\u7879 p gia. L\'fac \u273 \'f3 nghe n\'f3i th\u7913  \u273 ang th\u7871  th\'e2n "Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh" kia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \u7897 ng t\u297 nh g\'ec, ng\u432 \u7901 i Tr\'ec gia c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n tim Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917  \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7893 i. Nh\u432 ng con ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  s\u7889 ng m\'e3i trong th\'e2n x\'e1c qu\u7927  thi, th\u7901 i gian d\u7847 n qua Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u432 \u7905 ng trong v\u7887  b\u7885 c ho\u7841 t thi \u7903  Di\u7879 p gia b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u l\'e2m v\'e0o \u273 i\'ean cu\u7891 ng h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n, n\u7871 u n\'f3i \'f4ng m\u7899 i th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia t\u7917 , e r\u7857 ng c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng ai tin. Chuy\u7879 n c\u7913  k\'e9o d\'e0i m\'e3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ta c\u361 ng l\'e0 sau khi ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n Di\u7879 p gia m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c vi\u7879 c n\'e0y."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 "\uc0\u272 \'eam h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 A Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nghe l\u7847 m, Ph\'fac b\'e1 \u273 \'e3 th\u7853 t s\u7921  t\u7899 i, n\'f3i h\u7891 n ph\'e1ch Tr\'ec l\'e3o gia b\'e1m tr\'ean ho\u7841 t thi kia kh\'f4ng c\'f2n n\u7919 a, l\'e0 ta kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n em d\'ednh v\'e0o chuy\u7879 n Tr\'ec gia n\'ean m\u7899 i g\u7841 t em. A Di\'ean c\'f3 tr\'e1ch ca ca kh\'f4ng?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i xong nh\'ecn m\u7855 t c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  hi\u7875 u suy ngh\u297  c\'f9ng t\'ednh to\'e1n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tr\'e1ch h\u7855 n, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean nh\'ecn \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u \u273 en kia, l\u7841 i t\u7887  v\u7867  t\'f9y \'fd \u273 \u7893 i t\u7847 m m\u7855 t, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "... H\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i th\'ec kh\'f4ng tr\'e1ch ca ca."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec c\u7853 u b\u7879 nh, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7915  \u273 \'eam qua t\u7899 i gi\u7901  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n ki\u7873 m ch\u7871 , h\'f4n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m h\'f4n s\u7901  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m s\u7901 , \'f4m c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n. Nghe l\u7901 i n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u trong l\'f2ng v\u7915 a ng\u7885 t v\u7915 a t\u7913 c, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c tr\u7903  m\'ecnh ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y \u273 \'e8 Tr\'ec Di\'ean xu\u7889 ng: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng d\u432 \u7905 ng b\u7879 nh n\u7919 a, \u273 \u7875  ca ca th\u432 \u417 ng em."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 H\'f4n v\'e0i c\'e1i Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7849 y h\u7855 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, \u273 \u7915 ng l\'e0m em. Em c\'f2n c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i ca ca, c\'f2n ph\u7843 i \u273 i ch\u259 m ngo\u7841 i n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Ban \uc0\u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u c\'f2n \u273 \u7883 nh s\'e1ng s\u7899 m \u273 i thay T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i l\u7841 i b\u7883  b\u7879 nh k\'e9o d\'e0i t\u7899 i t\u7853 n tr\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe v\u7853 y, nh\'e0n nh\u7841 t li\u7871 c c\u7853 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i m\u7899 i ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y. H\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m t\u7881 nh, \u259 n m\u7863 c ch\u7881 nh t\u7873 , ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean mu\u7889 n r\u7901 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng li\u7873 n l\u7845 y t\u7915  trong t\u7911  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u m\u7897 t b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o, x\u7889 c ch\u259 n l\'ean m\u7863 c cho c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 H\uc0\u7855 n ng\u7891 i b\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, h\u417 i nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e0i c\'fac cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nghe Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7887 i: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, ca c\'f2n ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \'e2u. Th\u7913  kia r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 g\'ec, n\'f3 n\'f3i qu\u7927  kh\'ed k\'e9o d\'e0i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec? Trong nh\'e0 b\'ean kia v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng sao ch\u7913 , nh\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y sao r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7853 m r\'e3i c\'e0i c\'fac cho c\u7853 u: "Tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n lo th\u7913  kia l\'e0 ai hay c\'e1i g\'ec, n\'f3 mu\u7889 n duy tr\'ec s\u7921  s\u7889 ng \u7903  nh\'e2n gian c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7921 a v\'e0o vi\u7879 c \u273 o\u7841 t x\'e1 con ch\'e1u c\u7911 a t\u7893  ph\u7909 . Nh\u432 ng nh\u7841 c ph\u7909  l\'e0 con trai \u273 \u7897 c nh\u7845 t, l\u7841 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 em v\'e0 Tr\'ec Dung, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u417  th\u7875  Tr\'ec Dung v\'e0 em n\'f3 \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng d\'f9ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u417  th\u7875  nh\u7841 c ph\u7909  b\u7903 i v\'ec quanh n\u259 m b\u7883  c\u7893  \u273 \u7897 c \u259 n m\'f2n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c bao l\'e2u, n\'f3 ph\u7843 i g\u7845 p g\'e1p t\'ecm bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p kh\'e1c k\'e9o d\'e0i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng. Hi\u7879 n gi\u7901  qu\u7927  kh\'ed bao ph\u7911  b\'ean kia c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng d\'e0y, qu\u7927  kh\'ed tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i ta c\u361 ng c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng n\u7863 ng, n\'f3 b\'e8n cho r\u7857 ng ta l\'e0 d\u7921 a v\'e0o qu\u7927  kh\'ed \u7903  n\u417 i \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7875  duy tr\'ec s\u7921  s\u7889 ng n\'ean mu\u7889 n ta giao ra c\'e1ch th\u7913 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 N\'f3i \uc0\u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y th\'ec c\'e0i xong h\u7871 t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7915 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\u7847 m qu\u7847 n x\u7889 c ch\u259 n l\'ean chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c m\u7863 c cho c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i trong mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "Nh\u432 ng qu\u7927  kh\'ed tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i ta \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 do ta tu luy\u7879 n m\'e0 c\'f3, kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan g\'ec t\u7899 i qu\u7927  kh\'ed kia. N\'f3 \u273 \'e3 t\'ednh to\'e1n th\u7911  \u273 o\u7841 n, ch\u7881  c\'f2n ch\u7901  ta \u273 i, ti\u7871 c l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng tr\'f2 \u273 \'f3 v\'f4 d\u7909 ng v\u7899 i ta, sau khi em \u273 i ta tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p khi\u7871 n n\'f3 h\u7891 n phi ph\'e1ch t\'e1n. Chuy\u7879 n \u7903  H\u7913 a gia ta kh\'f4ng r\'f5 l\u7855 m, sau khi l\u7877  t\u7871  tr\u7901 i k\u7871 t th\'fac b\u7885 n h\u7885  thu x\u7871 p cho c\'e1c thi\'ean s\u432  t\u7899 i tham d\u7921  r\u7901 i \u273 i, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'f3ng k\'edn \u273 \u7841 i m\'f4n kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ra ngo\'e0i n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t mu\u7889 n c\u432 \u7899 p qu\u7847 n t\u7921  m\'ecnh m\u7863 c, v\u7873  sau l\u7841 i b\u7883  l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi thu h\'fat l\'e0m ho\'e0n to\'e0n qu\'ean m\u7845 t, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi nh\u7853 n ra th\'ec \u273 \'e3 xong xu\'f4i. C\u7853 u \'e1p mu b\'e0n tay l\'ean m\u7863 t, nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 h\u7841  s\u7889 t hay ch\u432 a: "V\u7853 y ca ca c\'f3 bi\u7871 t qu\u7927  kh\'ed kia l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 D\uc0\u7921 a theo t\'ecnh hu\u7889 ng \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia, c\'f3 qu\u7927  kh\'ed t\u7909  l\u7841 i l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec c\'f3 qu\u7927 . R\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u qu\u7927  ho\u7863 c m\u7897 t con qu\u7927  l\u7907 i h\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u t\u7841 o th\'e0nh hi\u7879 u qu\u7843  n\'e0y. M\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m sau \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \'edt t\u432  li\u7879 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\u7853 p b\'e1o c\'e1o \u273 \u432 a cho c\u7853 u xem, v\'ed d\u7909  nh\u432  khi b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i\u7873 u tra chuy\u7879 n th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \u273 \u7841 o s\u297 .\cb1 \
