\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, l\'fac c\'f2n tr\u7867  b\u7903 i v\'ec c\'f4ng t\'e1c n\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n th\'e0nh ph\u7889  n\'e0y, v\u7873  sau c\u432 \u7899 i b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i t\'ednh \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c an c\u432  l\u7841 c nghi\u7879 p. Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t sinh vi\'ean, giao thi\u7879 p v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u n\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i tham gia tang l\u7877  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7845 y, ch\u7881  c\'f3 v\'e0i b\u7841 n h\u7885 c th\'e2n thi\u7871 t \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng, m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\u7851 n gi\u7919  li\'ean l\u7841 c, hai h\u7885  h\'e0ng \u7903  qu\'ea t\u7899 i thay m\u7863 t v\'e0 m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7891 ng nghi\u7879 p \u273 \u7871 n gi\'fap c\u7911 a T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m. C\'f4ng vi\u7879 c ch\u7911  y\u7871 u v\u7851 n l\'e0 do ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i l\'e0m, h\u7871 t th\u7843 y \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t th\u7887 a \u273 \'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7902  tang l\u7877 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ho\'e0n to\'e0n \u273 \u7843 m nhi\u7879 m vai tr\'f2 con ch\'e1u trong nh\'e0 nh\u432  Tr\'ec Di\'ean, so v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\'f2n s\'e2u n\u7863 ng h\u417 n. \u272 \u7889 i v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ngo\'e0i \u273 \u7873 u n\'f3i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432  anh trai tr\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\u432 ng nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y \u7903  c\'f9ng nhau l\'e2u, v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m nh\'ecn ra quan h\u7879  c\u7911 a c\u7843  hai r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 g\'ec, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng c\'f3 ch\'fat ng\u432 \u7907 ng ng\'f9ng m\'e0 ng\u7847 m th\u7915 a nh\u7853 n v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 , cho n\'ean hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f4ng \u7893 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tang l\uc0\u7877  \u273 i qua ba ng\'e0y, t\'e2m tr\u7841 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7847 n \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7841 i, kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng y\'ean l\'f2ng, nh\u432 ng b\'ean Di\u7879 p gia n\'f3i x\u7843 y ra ch\'fat vi\u7879 c c\u7847 n h\u7855 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  x\u7917  l\'fd, Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7843 o h\u7855 n c\u7913  v\u7873 , nh\'e2n ti\u7879 n gi\'fap l\u432 u \'fd t\'ecnh h\'ecnh H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng xong nhanh ch\'f3ng quay tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e0 l\uc0\u7841 i ch\u7881  c\'f2n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \u273 i\u7875 m kh\'e1c duy nh\u7845 t l\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i n\u7919 a, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t b\'e0n th\u7901  trong ph\'f2ng ngo\u7841 i. Theo phong t\u7909 c th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, khi c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 t trong nh\'e0 ph\u7843 i th\u7855 p h\u432 \u417 ng \'edt nh\u7845 t b\u7843 y ng\'e0y m\u7899 i th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\uc0\u7879 c g\'ec l\'e0m, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 \u7885 an\u7857 m m\u7897 t m\'ecnh tr\'ean sofa \u7903  ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch xem TV, m\u417  m\u417  m\'e0ng m\'e0ng xong ng\u7911  m\u7845 t, TV v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 ang m\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'fac n\uc0\u7917 a t\u7881 nh n\u7917 a m\'ea nghe th\u7845 y c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i g\u7885 i t\'ean m\u7909  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i r\u7845 t quen thu\u7897 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t c\u7849 n th\u7853 n nghe, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u7843 o gi\'e1c, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \'e2m thanh TV truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u m\u7903  m\u7855 t, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c sofa nh\'ecn c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c t\u7881 nh h\u7859 n, c\'f3 ch\'fat do d\u7921  kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c m\'e0 nh\'ecn l\'e3o nh\'e2n quen thu\u7897 c tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t: "... Ngo\u7841 i, ngo\u7841 i \u417 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 X\'e1c nh\uc0\u7853 n ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c h\u7887 i: "Sao ngo\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  r\u7891 i? C\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u7841 ?" Tuy r\u7857 ng th\u432 \u417 ng nh\u7899  ngo\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng c\'f3 nh\u7919 ng nguy\'ean t\u7855 c c\u7853 u v\u7851 n hi\u7875 u r\'f5. \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873 , kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ch\'fat v\u432 \u417 ng v\u7845 n b\u7853 n l\'f2ng g\'ec m\'e0 \u273 i m\u7899 i l\'e0 t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, nh\'ecn d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0m sao: "Ngo\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t. Ngo\u7841 i... kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 n\'ean \u273 i r\u7891 i sao? T\u7841 i sao l\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Xem ra \'f4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i c\u361 ng hi\u7875 u t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, ch\u7881  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i th\u7859 ng ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\uc0\u7901 i \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng sofa, b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean tr\u7845 n an n\'f3i: "Ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7915 ng n\'f3ng v\u7897 i, \u273 \u7875  con ngh\u297  c\'e1ch."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i li\'ean t\u7909 c g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Ngo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng v\u7897 i, kh\'f4ng v\u7897 i. Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean c\u7913  t\u7915  t\u7915  suy ngh\u297 ."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 N\uc0\u7897 i t\'e2m Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7853 m r\'e3i x\'e2u chu\u7895 i manh m\u7889 i, sau khi tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u7853 u h\u7887 i th\u259 m nguy\'ean nh\'e2n \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7883  ng\u7845 t. \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i th\'edch \u259 n cua, h\u417 n n\u7919 a \u259 n r\u7845 t c\u7849 n th\u7853 n, ng\'e0y h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\'e0 \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean mua cua, bi\u7871 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u259 m s\'f3c tr\'f4ng nom n\'ean c\u7889  \'fd ch\u7885 n hai con to h\u7845 p ch\'edn r\u7891 i mang t\u7899 i cho ngo\u7841 i. L\'fac cua mang t\u7899 i v\u7851 n c\'f2n n\'f3ng, , \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i r\u7845 t vui v\u7867 , b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u259 n tr\'ean b\'e0n c\u417 m, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u chuy\'ean t\'e2m \u259 n h\u417 n n\u7917 a ti\u7871 ng, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  tho\'e1ng c\'e1i h\'f4n m\'ea b\u7845 t t\u7881 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cho n\'ean theo l\'fd m\'e0 n\'f3i, \'f4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i ra \u273 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n nu\u7889 i ti\u7871 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\u7887 i: "Ngo\u7841 i \u417 i, ngo\u7841 i c\'f2n mu\u7889 n g\u7863 p ai hay c\'f2n chuy\u7879 n g\'ec ch\u432 a y\'ean l\'f2ng hay sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o nh\'e2n nh\'ecn quanh m\uc0\u7897 t v\'f2ng trong nh\'e0, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3, Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh, ngo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f4ng y\'ean l\'f2ng. Sau n\'e0y con ph\u7843 i t\u7921  ch\u259 m s\'f3c b\u7843 n th\'e2n cho t\u7889 t, c\'f3 m\u7897 t gia \u273 \'ecnh ri\'eang, nh\u432  v\u7853 y ngo\u7841 i l\'e0 an t\'e2m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng k\'ecm l\'f2ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 l\u7841 i \u273 \u7887  v\'e0nh m\u7855 t: "... Hay \u273 \u7875  con th\u7917  ti\u7877 n ngo\u7841 i \u273 i?" \u7902  l\u7841 i d\u432 \u417 ng th\u7871  th\u7901 i gian d\'e0i s\u7869  b\u7845 t l\u7907 i cho vi\u7879 c v\'e3ng sinh, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n t\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e3o nh\'e2n kh\uc0\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t \'edt thu\u7853 t \u273 \u7897  vong \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n, c\u7853 u th\u7917  b\'e0y m\u7897 t ph\'e1p tr\u7853 n \u273 \u7897  vong trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, l\'e0m m\u7897 t nghi th\u7913 c ti\u7877 n \u273 \u432 a \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\'e3ng sinh. \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i im l\u7863 ng ng\u7891 i tr\'ean sofa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7893  h\u7885 ng chua x\'f3t kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i. Sau khi b\'e0 ngo\u7841 i v\'e0 m\u7865  qua \u273 \u7901 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 c\u7853 u v\'e0 \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng n\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 a v\'e0o nhau, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng hai l\u7847 n ti\u7877 n bi\u7879 t ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n nh\u7845 t. C\u7853 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i qu\u7923  g\u7889 i tr\u432 \u7899 c ph\'e1p tr\u7853 n, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n ni\u7879 m m\u7897 t c\'e2u ch\'fa v\u259 n \u273 \u7897  vong th\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t l\u7841 i r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng s\'e0n nh\'e0, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m nh\'ecn \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, s\u7907  s\u7921  th\u432 \u417 ng ti\u7871 c v\'e0 r\'e0ng bu\u7897 c n\'e0y s\u7869  c\u7843 n tr\u7903  ngo\u7841 i v\'e3ng sinh. Th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n xong to\'e0n b\u7897  nghi th\u7913 c c\u7853 u qu\u7923  s\u7909 p tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, g\u7847 n nh\u432  kh\'f3c kh\'f4ng th\'e0nh ti\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u nghe th\u7845 y gi\u7885 ng \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\'f4 c\'f9ng quen thu\u7897 c, mang theo nghi ho\u7863 c h\u7887 i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m xong ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361  \u273 ang ng\u7891 i \u7903  tr\'ean sofa, nh\u432  l\'e0 s\u7907  \u273 \'e3 qu\u7845 y r\u7847 y c\u7853 u "Thi ph\'e1p", th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \'f4\u803 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean x\uc0\u7845 u h\u7893  lu\u7889 ng cu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y: "... H\'ecnh nh\u432  th\u7845 t b\u7841 i r\u7891 i. Ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7915 ng lo l\u7855 ng, hay l\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean ngo\u7841 i c\u7913  ngh\u7881  trong nh\'e0 \u273 i, con c\'f3 quen m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n r\u7845 t gi\u7887 i, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7907 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 tr\u7903  v\u7873  l\u7841 i th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n l\u7841 i." Trong l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, s\u7921  th\u7853 t r\u7857 ng \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i qua \u273 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 phai nh\u7841 t, tuy r\u7857 ng c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t ngo\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, ch\u7881  l\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec nguy\'ean nh\'e2n kh\'f4ng r\'f5 n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 m\'e0 kh\'f4ng th\u7875  kh\'f4ng t\u7841 m th\u7901 i d\'f9ng m\u7897 t h\'ecnh th\'e1i kh\'e1c d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i n\u417 i n\'e0y, tr\u7843 i qua th\u7901 i gian ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 th\'edch \u7913 ng. Trong m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\u7851 n l\'e0 \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i, l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ai da, ngo\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng lo. \u272 \u7915 ng \u273 \u7875  b\u7841 n con ph\u7843 i v\u7897 i, \u273 \u7915 ng th\'fac ng\u432 \u7901 i ta." T\'e2m th\'e1i l\'e3o nh\'e2n l\u7841 i r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, m\u7897 t l\'e1t sau quay v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i nh\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng ng\'e0y, v\u7851 n duy tr\'ec th\'f3i quen l\'fac c\'f2n s\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7901  gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  n\'f3i ng\u7855 n g\u7885 n t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i vi\u7879 c c\u7913  ch\u7901  h\u7855 n, h\u7855 n r\u7845 t nhanh s\u7869  quay l\u7841 i, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng y\'ean l\'f2ng, quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh th\u7915 a d\u7883 p c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian \u273 \u7885 c cu\u7889 n b\'fat k\'ed m\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 a cho m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng s\uc0\u7899 m h\'f4m sau \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\u7841 i theo th\'f3i quen ra c\u7917 a. S\'e1ng s\u7899 m 7h30, tr\u432 \u7899 c kia \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\u7851 n lu\'f4n ra ngo\'e0i t\u7853 p bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng gi\u7901  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  sao c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u432  x\u432 a, Tr\'ec Di\'ean lo cho \'f4ng, c\u7847 m m\u7845 y t\u7845 m ph\'f9 v\'e0ng \u273 i theo. C\u7853 u th\u7845 y ngo\u7841 i quen b\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 theo sau \u273 \'e1m \u273 \'f4ng \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \'e8n xanh, b\u259 ng qua \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 i qua hai giao l\u7897  th\'ec \u273 \u7871 n c\'f4ng vi\'ean \u7903  qu\u7843 ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh. Ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 kh\'f4ng \'edt ng\u432 \u7901 i cao tu\u7893 i \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng, ngo\u7841 i th\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i quen mu\u7889 n \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n ch\'e0o h\u7887 i, nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y m\'ecnh m\u7899 i nh\u432  nh\u7899  ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, y\'ean l\u7863 ng lui sang m\u7897 t b\'ean, nh\'ecn m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'e1n g\u7851 u v\u7899 i nhau.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\'e1t sau m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7921  gi\'e1c x\u7871 p th\'e0nh \u273 \u7897 i ng\u361 , \u273 \u7913 ng th\'e0nh b\u7889 n h\'e0ng, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7853 p sau khi m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4 kh\u7849 u hi\u7879 u h\u432 \u7899 ng d\u7851 n "V\u7895  tay" . \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i c\u361 ng \u273 i theo \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  v\u7883  tr\'ed cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7911 a h\'e0ng cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng, c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y m\'e0 b\u7855 t theo nh\u7883 p c\u7911 a m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng sau \u273 \'ecnh ngh\u7881  m\'e1t nh\'ecn, l\'f2ng chua x\'f3t nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u7875  \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra m\'ecnh, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'fap ph\'eda sau l\'e9n l\'fat nh\'ecn, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n ch\'edn gi\u7901  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u t\u7853 p xong m\u7899 i theo ngo\u7841 i v\u7873  nh\'e0, l\'fac g\u7847 n v\u7873  \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 th\'ec \u273 i nhanh v\'e0i b\u432 \u7899 c v\'e0o nh\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c, gi\u7843  v\u7901  nh\u432  chuy\u7879 n g\'ec c\u361 ng ch\u432 a x\u7843 y ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m sau \'f4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i v\u7851 n nh\u432  c\u361  \u273 i ra c\'f4ng vi\'ean t\u7853 p theo m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i l\u7863 ng l\u7869  theo m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng cho \u273 \u7871 n khi ngo\u7841 i an to\'e0n v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u259 n c\u417 m, hai ng\'e0y n\'e0y l\u7841 i n\'f3i r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  n\'f3i bao nhi\'eau c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7871 t m\'e0 n\'f3i cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe. B\u7903 i v\'ec bi\u7871 t th\u7901 i gian kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u, b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, l\'fac n\'e0y th\u7901 i gian \'f4ng ch\'e1u \u7903  chung m\u7899 i th\u7845 y \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t \u273 \'e1ng qu\'fd, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7907 t gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh, \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t l\'e2u c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e0nh th\u7901 i gian \u7903  c\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i ngo\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e0y th\uc0\u7913  ba Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i theo ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n c\'f4ng vi\'ean, c\u7853 u v\u7851 n nh\u432  hai ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7891 i trong \u273 \'ecnh l\u7863 ng l\u7869  ch\'fa \'fd ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng trong s\'e2n, nh\u432 ng h\'f4m nay v\u7915 a ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng li\u7873 n ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i v\u7915 a \u273 i t\u7899 i s\'e2n ch\u7907 t c\'f3 m\u7845 y c\u7909  \'f4ng c\u7909  b\'e0 nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh v\'e2y quanh, ni\u7873 m n\u7903  h\u7887 i th\u259 m. \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'f3, r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\'f3 v\u7867  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  ng\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean v\u7873  nh\'e0 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 i t\u7899 i, \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y \'f4ng c\u7909  h\u7887 i "L\'e3o T\'f4 \'e0, d\u7841 o n\'e0y sao kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y", "B\u7883  b\u7879 nh hay sao, t\'f4i nghe n\'f3i h\'ecnh nh\u432  \'f4ng nh\u7853 p vi\u7879 n r\u7891 i m\'e0".\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7841 y nhanh \u273 \u7871 n \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i n\'f3i: "Ngo\u7841 i \'e0, mau c\'f9ng con v\u7873  nh\'e0 th\'f4i, s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e ch\u432 a t\u7889 t th\'ec ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7915 ng ch\u7841 y ra ngo\'e0i ch\u7913 ." C\'e1c c\u7909  \'f4ng c\u7909  b\'e0 n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7853 p \u7903  m\u7845 y c\'f4ng vi\'ean g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai tham gia tang l\u7877  c\u7911 a ngo\u7841 i, nh\u432 ng th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R r\u7845 t nh\u7887 , kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c l\'e0 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 nghe tin \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i qua \u273 \u7901 i nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ngo\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng d\'e1m x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh. \u272 \u7873  tr\'e1nh sinh th\'eam r\u7855 c r\u7889 i, t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'e0 n\'ean s\u7899 m r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1c c\uc0\u7909  nghe Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i v\u7853 y b\'e8n nhanh nh\u7843 u chen nhau n\'f3i "L\'e0 ch\'e1u ngo\u7841 i l\'e3o T\'f4 \'e0" "Th\u7853 t l\'e0 hi\u7871 u th\u7843 o, l\'e3o T\'f4 mau v\u7873  c\'f9ng ch\'e1u \u273 i, kh\u7887 e r\u7891 i l\u7841 i t\u7899 i" ... Tr\'ec Di\'ean mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng c\u432 \u7901 i c\u7843 m \u417 n m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 \u432 a ngo\u7841 i v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i nghi ho\u7863 c nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean \'e0, sao m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e3o L\'fd l\u7841 i th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngo\u7841 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Con c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 l\u7855 m, ch\'fang ta c\u7913  \u273 \u7907 i b\u7841 n con tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 \'e3, h\u7855 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t. Nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y ngo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'ean ra c\u7917 a." M\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\u7853 u cho r\u7857 ng ch\u7881  m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y ngo\u7841 i l\'e0 v\'ec hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 quan h\u7879  huy\u7871 t th\u7889 ng, b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 i tu t\u7853 p thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p t\u7915 ng g\u7863 p ma qu\u7927  t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i nhi\u7873 u. Nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ngo\u7841 i, \u273 i\u7873 u n\'e0y l\'e0m c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y r\u7845 t kh\'f3 hi\u7875 u. C\u7853 u l\u7853 t xem b\'fat k\'fd Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i cho m\'ecnh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gi\u7843 i th\'edch h\u7907 p l\'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u259 n t\u7889 i xong T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7841 i t\u7899 i th\u259 m. L\'fac nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng chu\'f4ng c\u7917 a \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i li\u7873 n tr\'e1nh v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng, \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7915 a tan t\u7847 m, \u273 ang mu\u7889 n v\'e0o th\u7855 p h\u432 \u417 ng cho ngo\u7841 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'e0o d\'e1m \u273 \u7875  h\u7855 n \u273 i v\'e0o, chung quy th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o gi\u7843 i th\'edch t\u7841 i sao \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n, h\u417 n n\u7919 a t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, lo\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ai c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n, cho n\'ean c\u7853 u b\'e8n b\u7883 a v\'e0i l\'ed do k\'e9o T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ra ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch ng\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n l\'e0 bi\u7871 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  nh\'e0 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f2n n\'ean sau khi tan l\'e0m c\u7889  \'fd t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y h\'e0n huy\'ean, xem tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i c\u7853 u th\u7871  n\'e0o, th\u7845 y tinh th\u7847 n c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng t\u7879  l\u7855 m c\u361 ng y\'ean l\'f2ng, tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\u7841 i n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m n\'e2ng ch\'e9n tr\'e0 u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , c\u7853 u n\'f3i c\'f3 xem c\'f3 l\u7841  kh\'f4ng, b\u7885 n t\'f4i v\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t v\u7909  \'e1n m\u7845 t t\'edch, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'e1o \'e1n l\'e0 v\u7907  c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 t t\'edch, c\'f4 \u7845 y n\'f3i ch\u7891 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t t\'edch hai ng\'e0y, t\'ecm th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\u7885 n t\'f4i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thi th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i \u7903  m\u7897 t nh\'e0 tr\u7885 , c\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o k\u7871 t qu\u7843  ki\'ea\u777 m tra thi th\'ea\u777 , ch\u7891 ng c\u7911 a c\'f4 \u7845 y \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  gi\u7871 t b\u7843 y ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
