\f1\b0 \cf2 C\'e2u n\'f3i n\'e0y nh\uc0\u432  m\u7897 t qu\u7843  ch\'f9y, t\u7915 ng ch\u7919  m\u7897 t d\u7897 i v\'e0o tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \u7853 p m\u7841 nh, d\u7921  c\u7843 m x\u7845 u d\'e2ng l\'ean trong c\u7893 , c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y cu\u7889 ng h\u7885 ng kh\'f4 l\u7841 i, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ch\u7881  nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng, v\u7909  \'e1n n\'e0y r\u7845 t b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t c\u7853 u t\'ecm c\u7899  kh\'f4ng tham gia \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? Xin ngh\u7881  \u7903  nh\'e0 m\u7845 y h\'f4m ch\u259 m s\'f3c Quy\'ean Quy\'ean ch\u7859 ng h\u7841 n." C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng lo \u273 \u432 \u7907 c cho qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u hy v\u7885 ng b\u7841 n b\'e8 quanh m\'ecnh \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  b\'ecnh an.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i ngay: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , \'fd c\u7853 u l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7913  kia qu\u7845 y ph\'e1? \u7914 m... T\'f4i s\u7869  n\'f3i v\u7899 i s\u432  ph\u7909 , c\u361 ng s\u7869  ch\'fa \'fd h\u417 n, c\u7853 u y\'ean t\'e2m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\uc0\u7903  d\'e0i, hi\u7875 u r\u7857 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\u7877  d\'e0ng r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i v\u7883  tr\'ed c\'f4ng t\'e1c, hu\u7889 ng chi m\'ecnh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ch\u7855 c tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t \u273 \'fang nh\u432  m\'ecnh ngh\u297 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t khuy\'ean nh\u7911  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, \u273 \'e0nh tr\'f2 chuy\u7879 n th\'eam \u273 \'f4i c\'e2u v\u7899 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, h\u7887 i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean v\'e0 b\'e0o thai trong b\u7909 ng g\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y, sau \u273 \'f3 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m t\u7841 m bi\u7879 t c\u7853 u r\u7891 i \u273 i v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i t\u7915  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u273 i ra, ch\u7855 p tay sau l\u432 ng b\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n ban c\'f4ng ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, nh\'ecn s\u7855 c tr\u7901 i b\'ean ngo\'e0i l\u7849 m b\u7849 m: "S\u7855 p m\u432 a r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f9a n\'e0y th\'e0nh ph\uc0\u7889  R v\u7889 n nhi\u7873 u m\u432 a, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 ang r\u7917 a ch\'e9n T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m d\'f9ng thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng \u273 \'e1p: "Kh\'f4ng sao \u273 \'e2u ngo\u7841 i, \u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng c\'f3 xe r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i n\'f3i kh\'f4ng sai, \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 m\u432 a t\u7847 m t\'e3 tr\'fat xu\u7889 ng th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R. Tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng h\u7847 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i, ngay c\u7843  xe c\u7897  c\u361 ng \'edt h\u417 n m\u7885 i khi r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u, n\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng m\u432 a n\u7863 ng h\u7841 t kh\'f4ng d\u7913 t, ti\u7871 ng \'f4 t\'f4 th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng ch\u7841 y qua r\u7869  n\u432 \u7899 c '\'c0o \'c0o' c\'f9ng v\u7899 i ti\u7871 ng c\'e2y c\u7889 i rung l\u7855 c trong gi\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7919 a \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i \'e2m thanh h\u7895 n t\u7841 p b\'ean ngo\'e0i, b\'ean trong l\u7841 i c\'e0ng tr\u7903  n\'ean y\'ean t\u297 nh, ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a ch\u7907 t truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng g\'f5 c\u7917 a theo nh\u7883 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y \uc0\u273 ang l\'e0 n\u7917 a \u273 \'eam, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'ec ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n c\'e2u n\'f3i kia c\u7911 a T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m m\'e0 m\'e3i kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 ang c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i ch\u417 i, nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c d\u7915 ng \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c tr\'ean tay, nghi\'eang tai c\u7849 n th\u7853 n nghe\'97\'97 th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang g\'f5 c\u7917 a nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, tr\u7903  m\'ecnh xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch t\u7889 i om, b\u7909 ng h\u417 i b\u7845 t an l\u7841 i c\'f3 v\'e0i ph\u7847 n ch\u7901  mong. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean m\u7903  c\'e1nh c\u7917 a g\u7895 , th\'f4ng qua m\u7855 t m\'e8o tr\'ean c\u7917 a ch\u7889 ng tr\u7897 m nh\'ecn ra ngo\'e0i, tho\'e1ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  \u273 en cao g\u7847 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\u7883 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'e2ng kh\'f3e m\'f4i, m\u7897 t tay m\u7903  c\u7917 a ch\u7889 ng tr\u7897 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'ed l\uc0\u7841 nh c\'f9ng h\u417 i n\u432 \u7899 c theo nam nh\'e2n tr\'e0n v\'e0o. H\u7855 n tr\u7903  tay g\'e0i c\u7917 a l\u7841 i, v\u7915 a \u273 \u7871 n huy\u7873 n quan l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \'f4m c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng thu\u7853 n th\u7871  \'f4m l\u7841 i h\u7855 n, c\'f3 ch\'fat \u7927  l\u7841 i m\'e0 d\'e1n l\'ean h\u7855 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, sao mu\u7897 n th\u7871  n\'e0y r\u7891 i c\'f2n t\u7899 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi "\u7914 " r\u7891 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i, h\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i: "Sao mu\u7897 n th\u7871  n\'e0y c\'f2n ch\u432 a ng\u7911 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i v\u7851 n \u273 ang ng\u7911  trong ph\'f2ng, theo l\'fd m\'e0 n\'f3i b\'e2y gi\u7901  ngo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ng\u7911  n\u7919 a, nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  t\u7853 p th\u7875  d\u7909 c bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng, ngo\u7841 i v\u7851 n duy tr\'ec th\'f3i quen ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\u7907  l\'e0m \u7891 n \u273 \u7871 n ngo\u7841 i b\'e8n k\'e9o Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7873  ph\'f2ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng ng\uc0\u7911  kh\'f4ng b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7885 c s\'e1ch \u273 ang m\u7903  \u273 \u7863 t tr\'ean b\'e0n. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7903 i \'e1o kho\'e1c treo v\'e0o t\u7911  qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u c\u7903 i n\'fat \'e1o s\u417 mi, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7903 i gi\'fap h\u7855 n, v\u7915 a c\u7903 i v\u7915 a n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng ng\uc0\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c..." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7855 c l\u7841 i l\u7901 i c\u7853 u, h\u417 i ng\u7917 a ng\u432 \u7901 i ra sau, trong m\u361 i kh\u7869  h\u7915  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, du\u7895 i tay \u7845 n l\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\'e3 xu\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh, "\u7914 , v\u7853 y \u273 \'eam nay h\u7843 o h\u7843 o h\u7847 u h\u7841  ca ca l\'e0 ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\uc0\u7913 c h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t h\u7885 c \u7903  \u273 \'e2u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7855 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, song l\u7841 i \u273 au l\'f2ng b\u7879 nh t\'ecnh c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, d\'f9 sao c\u417  th\u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i thu\u7853 n theo h\u7855 n, gi\u7853 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng n\u7905  gi\u7853 n. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mu\u7889 n c\'e1i g\'ec th\'ec cho c\'e1i \u273 \'f3, \u273 \u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7853 n h\u7913 ng, l\'e0m \u273 i l\'e0m l\u7841 i r\u7845 t l\'e2u, m\'e0 sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'fang l\'e0 ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7853 t nh\u432  l\u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, h\u417 n n\u7919 a ng\u7911  r\u7845 t ngon.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tham ng\u7911 , s\'e1ng 8h30 \u273 \'e3 r\u7901 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng, t\'ednh ra ng\u7911  ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n ba ti\u7871 ng. C\u7853 u gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi cho ngo\u7841 i, n\'f3i cho ngo\u7841 i bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n r\u7845 t gi\u7887 i m\'e0 c\u7853 u nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec b\u7845 t ng\u7901  x\u7843 y ra th\'ec hai ng\'e0y n\'e0y s\u7869  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 a ngo\u7841 i \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u258 n s\'e1ng xong Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7917 a b\'e1t trong b\u7871 p m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i im l\u7863 ng \u273 i t\u7899 i, \u273 \u7913 ng sau c\u7853 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean \'e0, con n\'f3i cho ngo\u7841 i nghe, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n kia c\u7911 a con r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c lai l\u7883 ch th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean suy ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \'e1p: "Nh\'e0 anh \u7845 y gi\u7889 ng Tr\'ec gia, c\u361 ng l\'e0m thi\'ean s\u432 . Nh\u432 ng anh \u7845 y gi\u7887 i h\u417 n g\'e0 m\u7901  nh\u432  con nhi\u7873 u, t\'ednh t\'ecnh c\u361 ng r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, l\u7899 n l\'ean c\'f9ng con t\u7915  nh\u7887 , ngo\u7841 i y\'ean t\'e2m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong con ng\uc0\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7909 c ng\u7847 u c\u7911 a ngo\u7841 i v\u7851 n hi\u7879 n v\u7867  lo l\u7855 ng: "Nh\u432 ng Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean \'e0, ngo\u7841 i nh\'ecn con, nh\'ecn l\'e3o L\'fd, ti\u7875 u T\u7889 ng, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 nh\'e2n d\u7841 ng, l\'e0 h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i; nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ra ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n kia c\u7911 a con l\'e0 h\'ecnh g\'ec, ngo\u7841 i ch\u7881  th\u7845 y m\u7897 t kh\u7889 i \u273 en \u273 \u7863 c, ch\u7881  to\'e0n qu\u7927  kh\'ed v\'e0 \'e2m kh\'ed... Ngo\u7841 i s\u7907 , ngo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 i c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7847 u thai c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\u432 ng Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, con nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'ec ngo\u7841 i m\'e0 ch\u7885 c v\'e0o th\u7913  kh\'f4ng n\'ean ch\u7885 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng tr\u7845 n an: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec m\'e0, ngo\u7841 i \u273 \u7915 ng lo qu\'e1, nh\'e0 anh \u7845 y tu qu\u7927  \u273 \u7841 o, tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn h\u417 i kh\'e1c nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  g\'ec \u273 \'e2u." Hu\u7889 ng h\u7891  chuy\u7879 n ch\u7885 c v\'e0o g\'ec \u273 \'f3, cho d\'f9 kh\'f4ng v\'ec chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a ngo\u7841 i th\'ec c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m ch\u7885 c ph\u7843 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7887  v\u7867  th\'e2n thi\u7871 t tin t\u432 \u7903 ng l\u7841 i nghe c\u7853 u gi\u7843 i th\'edch nh\u432  v\u7853 y, v\u7867  lo l\u7855 ng trong m\u7855 t ngo\u7841 i tho\'e1ng nh\u7841 t \u273 i, nh\u432 ng m\u7897 t m\u7889 i lo kh\'e1c trong l\'f2ng l\u7841 i l\u7899 n th\'eam\'97\'97 \u273 \'e2y ch\u7881  l\'e0 tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c c\u7911 a ngo\u7841 i, tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 th\u7913  g\'ec t\u7889 t, ch\'e1u ngo\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh th\'e2n c\u7853 n th\u7913  kia nh\u432  v\u7853 y, ch\u7881  s\u7907  s\u7869  b\u7883  \u259 n \u273 \u7871 n m\u7849 u v\u7909 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  b\u7903 i v\'ec d\u7921  c\u7843 m b\u7845 t an m\'e0 khuy\'ean T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m t\u7841 m ng\u7915 ng c\'f4ng t\'e1c, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ch\u7881  d\u7921 a v\'e0o tr\u7921 c gi\'e1c m\'e0 khuy\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean tr\'e1nh xa Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, cho n\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  c\u7853 u c\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \u273 \u7915 ng qu\'e1 tin t\u432 \u7903 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n ti\u7877 n ngo\u7841 i \u273 i kh\'f4ng n\'ean ch\u7853 m tr\u7877 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\'e0n b\u7841 c tranh th\u7911  ban \u273 \'eam gi\u7901  T\'fd
\f2\i  (23h-1h)
\f1\i0  s\uc0\u7869  \u273 \u432 a ngo\u7841 i \u273 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7887 i \'fd ki\u7871 n ngo\u7841 i, ngo\u7841 i c\u361 ng \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd, ch\u7881  l\'e0 v\u7851 n c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng an l\'f2ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, l\u7841 i d\u7863 n d\'f2 c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n, ch\u259 m s\'f3c t\u7889 t ch\'ednh m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean thi\uc0\u7871 u v\'e0i th\u7913  c\u7847 n thi\u7871 t \u273 \u7875  b\'e0y ph\'e1p tr\u7853 n, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi cho ng\u432 \u7901 i mang t\u7899 i. Nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n c\'f3 v\u7867  kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n thu\u7897 c h\u7841  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'e0o nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean, mu\u7889 n t\u7921  m\'ecnh xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7845 y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'f3i \u273 i thay h\u7855 n c\u361 ng b\u7883  t\u7915  ch\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i \u273 i m\u7897 t ph\'fat l\u7841 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n g\'f5 c\u7917 a, ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7853 p c\u7917 a d\u7891 n d\u7853 p, kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quay l\u7841 i. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi ho\u7863 c kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7899 i l\'e0 ai, m\u7903  m\u7897 t b\'ean c\u7917 a, b\u7903 i v\'ec m\u7899 i ch\u7841 ng v\u7841 ng t\u7889 i, h\'e0ng x\'f3m \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  nh\'e0, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng k\u7867  x\u7845 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y n\'ean c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7843 nh gi\'e1c qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i c\uc0\u7917 a l\'e0 m\u7897 t thanh ni\'ean t\'f3c tai r\u7889 i b\'f9, qu\u7847 n \'e1o nh\u259 n nh\'fam, d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7855 t th\'e2m qu\u7847 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn hai l\u7847 n m\u7899 i x\'e1c nh\u7853 n ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t h\'f3a ra l\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  r\u7845 t k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng, nhanh ch\'f3ng x\'f4ng v\'e0o trong c\u7917 a, t\u7921 a h\u7891  \u273 ang s\u7907  th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng kh\'f3a c\u7917 a ch\u7889 ng tr\u7897 m r\u7891 i m\u7899 i d\'e3n m\u7897 t h\u417 i th\u7853 t d\'e0i, m\u7855 t nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n h\u417 i \u273 \u7887  nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng c\u432 \u7901 i: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c t\'f4i c\u361 ng tr\u7889 n ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7845 y cho h\u7855 n c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c \u7845 m, b\u7843 o h\u7855 n ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng gh\u7871 : "Sao th\u7871 ? C\u7913  t\u7915  t\u7915  n\'f3i, \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f4i H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y run run, nh\'ecn h\u417 i n\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0u tr\u7855 ng b\u7889 c l\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t, \'e1nh m\u7855 t v\'f4 \u273 \u7883 nh: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f2n n\u7919 a... t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903  H\u7913 a gia, Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n r\u7901 i \u273 i t\u7915  s\u7899 m hay t\'f4i tr\u7889 n ra \u273 \'e2y, \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean t\'f3m ch\u7863 t tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean lay m\u7841 nh: "Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n....! Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7919 a r\u7891 i! N\'fai \u7849 n tr\u7903  th\'e0nh c\'e1i d\u7841 ng kia, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 v\'ec h\u7855 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u417 i d\'f2ng h\u7885  Di\u7879 p, Tr\'ec, H\u7913 a \u7849 n c\u432 , \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i ba nh\'e0 g\u7885 i l\'e0 n\'fai \u7849 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7913 ng l\u7841 i, tay H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y r\u7845 t l\u7841 nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh nh\u432  b\u7883  m\u7897 t kh\u7889 i b\u259 ng t\'f3m ch\u7863 t, l\'f2ng b\'e0n tay \u273 \'e3 ch\u7843 y m\u7891  h\'f4i. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian b\u7853 n t\'e2m, b\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i tay H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng h\u7855 n n\'f3i: "C\u7853 u n\'f3i c\'e1i g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i. N\'fai \u7849 n qu\u7927  kh\'ed d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c, \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng ngh\u7883 ch \u273 \u7843 o nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 v\'ec h\u7855 n. A Di\'ean c\u7853 u ph\u7843 i tin t\'f4i, b\u7885 n t\'f4i t\'ecm th\u7845 y m\u7897  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi trong ph\u7847 n m\u7897  t\u7893  ti\'ean Di\u7879 p gia, l\'fac \u273 \'f3 \u273 ang mu\u7889 n \u273 \'e0o m\u7897  nghi\u7879 m quan t\'e0i th\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7903  v\u7873 , sau \u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p gia b\u7855 t h\u7871 t b\u7885 n t\'f4i l\u7841 i, nh\u7901  c\'f3 cha m\u7865  v\u7899 i b\'e1c c\u7843  tr\u7907  gi\'fap t\'f4i m\u7899 i ch\u7841 y ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\'ecnh t\'f4i ch\u7841 y tho\'e1t... Tr\'ec Di\'ean, t\'f4i t\u7853 n m\u7855 t th\u7845 y r\u7891 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e2u." Tay h\u7855 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n run r\u7849 y, n\'f3i n\u259 ng c\u361 ng l\u7897 n x\u7897 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7895  v\u7895  h\u7855 n: "H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, c\u7853 u b\'ecnh t\u297 nh m\u7897 t ch\'fat, t\u7915  t\u7915  n\'f3i. L\u7901 i c\u7853 u n\'f3i r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 sao? T\u7841 i sao n\'f3i qu\u7927  kh\'ed \u7903  n\'fai l\'e0 v\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi? C\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec m\'e0 ph\u7843 i m\u7903  quan t\'e0i?" Tr\u7841 ng th\'e1i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\'fac n\'e0y r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \u7897  tin c\u7853 y c\u361 ng gi\u7843 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng tin Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, cho n\'ean chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y h\u7859 n l\'e0 c\'f3 hi\u7875 u l\u7847 m, ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7907 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y gi\u7843 i th\'edch m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 "L\'e0... T\'f4i k\uc0\u7875  l\u7841 i suy \u273 o\'e1n ban \u273 \u7847 u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u cho cha t\'f4i nghe, \'f4ng \u7845 y v\'e0 b\'e1c c\u7843  d\'f9ng ph\'e1p kh\'ed trong nh\'e0 quan s\'e1t, n\'fai \u7849 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  t\u7847 ng m\u7897 t qu\u7927  kh\'ed d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c bao v\'e2y, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  tra ra ngu\u7891 n c\u7911 a qu\u7927  kh\'ed ngay t\u7841 i Di\u7879 p gia, tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe l\uc0\u7901 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean nh\u7899  t\u7899 i l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c th\u7913  m\u432 \u7907 n x\'e1c Tr\'ec L\'e2m Sinh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\'e0 qu\u7927  kh\'ed ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 li\'ean quan. Nh\u432 ng th\u7913  kia n\'f3i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7921 a v\'e0o h\u7845 p th\u7909  qu\u7927  kh\'ed \u273 \u7875  k\'e9o d\'e0i t\'ednh m\u7841 ng, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u432 \u7907 n qu\u7927  kh\'ed m\'e0 s\u7889 ng; m\'e0 \'fd trong l\u7901 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\u7841 i l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\'e0 ngu\u7891 n g\'e2y qu\u7927  kh\'ed, qu\u7927  kh\'ed b\u7903 i v\'ec Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\'e0 sinh. Hai l\u7901 i n\'e0y m\'e2u th\u7851 n v\u7899 i nhau, ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n c\'f3 m\u7897 t ph\'e1n \u273 o\'e1n sai ho\u7863 c c\u7843  hai \u273 \u7873 u sai. Nh\u432 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca v\'e0 qu\u7927  kh\'ed kia th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 li\'ean quan, ch\u7901  h\u7855 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\u7843 i h\u7887 i r\'f5 r\'e0ng m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i nghe H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "Nh\u432 ng ma qu\u7927  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0o c\'f3 th\u7875  g\'e2y \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng v\'e0 m\u7841 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7909 y trang th\'e0nh thi\'ean s\u432  nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m m\'e0 kh\'f4ng b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u7843 i bi\u7871 n s\u7889  m\u7879 nh m\u7897 t v\'f9ng linh \u273 \u7883 a, bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh c\u7843 nh t\u432 \u7907 ng \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\'ean \u273 \u7843 o. B\'e1c c\u7843  v\'e0 cha t\'f4i ho\'e0i nghi Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi sau khi ch\u7871 t \u273 \'e3 h\'f3a th\'e0nh \u272 \u7871  Ho\'e0ng qu\u7927  c\u7921 c \'e1c c\u7921 c t\'e0 tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng c\'f3, v\'ec \u273 \u7875  nghi\u7879 m ch\u7913 ng \u273 i\u7875 m n\'e0y, c\u361 ng \u273 \u7875  t\u259 ng th\'eam l\u7907 i th\u7871  \u273 \u7889 i ph\'f3 h\u7855 n n\'ean \u273 \'e3 \'e2m th\u7847 m t\'ecm ki\u7871 m huy\u7879 t m\u7897  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 tr\u7845 n t\u297 nh h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u, l\u7901 i n\'f3i c\u361 ng m\u7841 nh l\u7841 c h\u417 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n nh\'edu m\'e0y y\'ean l\u7863 ng nghe, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i t\u7915  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  th\'f2 ra n\u7917 a ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\u7863 ng l\u7869  v\u7851 y tay v\u7873  ph\'eda c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 ang \u273 \u432 a l\u432 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda ngo\u7841 i n\'ean kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y nh\'e9t c\u7889 c tr\'e0 n\'f3ng v\'e0o tay H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y: "C\u7853 u ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t l\'fac cho \u7845 m \u273 i, t\'f4i \u273 i v\u7879  sinh."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, c\u7847 m c\u7889 c tr\'e0 ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, trong m\u7855 t kh\'f3 n\'e9n s\u7921  m\u7879 t m\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7841 nh ngo\u7841 i, l\'e3o nh\'e2n k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, con c\u7849 n th\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i nh\u7853 n ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n n\'e0y c\u7911 a con gi\u7889 ng ngo\u7841 i, \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
