\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u417  ng\'e1c, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng h\u7887 i l\u7841 i: "Ngo\u7841 i n\'f3i... H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\uc0\u7841 i n\u7863 ng n\u7873  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u. \'d4ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\'ec sao l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873 , \'f4ng ch\u7881  hi v\u7885 ng ch\'e1u ngo\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\u7875  tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i n\'e0y, s\u7889 ng m\u7897 t \u273 \u7901 i b\'ecnh an.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c tr\u7903  l\u7841 i ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7911 a H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, h\u7855 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p n\u7841 n. H\u7855 n cho r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i duy nh\u7845 t "Tr\u7889 n tho\'e1t" \u7903  H\u7913 a gia.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 ang ng\u7891 i b\u7845 m di \u273 \u7897 ng \u7903  ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, th\u7845 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay l\u7841 i thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "Tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac \u273 i t\'f4i g\u7917 i tin nh\u7855 n cho Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n r\u7891 i m\u7899 i b\u7855 t xe \u273 i t\'ecm c\u7853 u, con b\'e9 lo l\u7855 m, h\u7887 i t\'f4i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh H\u7913 a gia th\u7871  n\'e0o." N\'f3i c\'e2u cu\u7889 i xong gi\u7885 ng h\u7855 n tr\u7903  n\'ean \u7843 m \u273 \u7841 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i H\u7913 a gia r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 b\u7883  l\'e0m sao?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7871 t h\u7871 t r\u7891 i. Nh\u432 ng gi\u7889 ng Tr\'ec Dung l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n h\u7891 n ph\'e1ch v\u7851 n c\'f2n th\'ec c\u7913  \u7903  trong n\'fai \u7849 n c\'f3 qu\u7927  kh\'ed \'e2m kh\'ed d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c l\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  sinh ho\u7841 t nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, th\u7853 m ch\'ed r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t. Nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u ra kh\u7887 i khu v\u7921 c qu\u7927  kh\'ed bao ph\u7911  s\u7869  d\u7877  d\'e0ng hi\u7879 n nguy\'ean h\'ecnh, ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 y c\u7853 u c\'f3 bi\u7871 t r\u7857 ng th\u7853 t ra c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t kh\'f4ng? Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, trong ng\u7921 c l\u7841 i nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'e2ng l\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c bi ai, ngay sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y to\'e0n th\'e2n l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o, m\u7897 t \'fd ngh\u297  c\u7921 c k\u7923  \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  l\'f3e l\'ean trong \u273 \u7847 u \'97\'97 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \u7903  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t m\'ecnh nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t b\u7843 n th\'e2n \u273 \'e3 qua \u273 \u7901 i, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7909  \'e1n k\'ec l\u7841  gi\u7889 ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p L\'e2m Tr\u7909  M\'e3 Thi\'ean, \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i r\'f5 r\'e0ng \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t l\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  \u273 \'e2y, th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'e1c l\'e3o nh\'e2n luy\u7879 n c\'f4ng bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y ngo\u7841 i... Li\u7879 u c\'f3 ph\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec n\u417 i m\'ecnh \u273 ang s\u7889 ng l\'fac n\'e0y, c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh n\u417 i qu\u7927  kh\'ed d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c, \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng ngh\u7883 ch \u273 \u7843 o nh\u432  n\'fai \u7849 n, nh\u432  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n xu\u7845 t th\u7847 n, ch\u7907 t nghe H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\'f3i: "\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, Tr\'ec thi\u7871 u, c\'f3 m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\u7853 u t\u7915 ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i ch\u432 a?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi\'eang \uc0\u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u c\u7853 u t\u7853 n tim, n\u259 m c\u7853 u v\'e0o \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c h\u7855 n l\'ean l\'e0m gia ch\u7911  Di\u7879 p gia, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\'f3 kh\u7843  n\u259 ng \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u v\u7873  ho\u7863 c t\u7921  m\'ecnh \u273 i th\u259 m c\u7853 u, v\'ec c\u7899  g\'ec l\u7841 i b\u7887  m\u7863 c c\u7853 u \u7903  b\'ean ngo\'e0i nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, m\u7897 t ch\'fat quan t\'e2m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng k\u7883 p, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i ti\u7871 p: "Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia t\'f4i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u, nh\u432 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ngh\u297  th\'f4ng su\u7889 t. B\u7903 i v\'ec h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i, nh\u432 ng l\'fac \u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n m\u7899 i ch\u7871 t, qu\u7927  kh\'ed ch\u432 a d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 , h\u7855 n s\u7907  l\u7897  ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng, b\u7883  c\u7853 u ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t. M\'e0 b\'e2y gi\u7901  h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 em to\'e0n b\u7897  th\u7871  gi\u7899 i \u273 \u7843 o ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  d\'e1m kh\'f4ng ki\'eang k\u7925  g\'ec m\'e0 \u7903  c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u n\'f3i c\u7909 c di\u7879 n \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng ngh\u7883 ch \u273 \u7843 o \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 do Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca t\u7841 o th\'e0nh?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, "Kh\'f4ng th\u7875 , Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  th\u7871 , anh \u7845 y s\u7869  kh\'f4ng v\'f4 c\u7899  t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "\u272 \'fang, h\u7855 n ch\u7855 c l\'e0 s\u7869  kh\'f4ng v\'f4 c\u7899  t\u7893 n th\u432 \u417 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c. *Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o kh\'f4ng gi\u7871 t B\'e1 Nh\'e2n, B\'e1 Nh\'e2n l\u7841 i v\'ec V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o m\'e0 ch\u7871 t, d\u432 \u7899 i t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\'ean \u273 \u7843 o, \'e1c qu\u7927  sinh s\'f4i, h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t m\u7841 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  si\'eau \u273 \u7897 , cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng tr\u7903  th\'e0nh \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c tr\u7847 n gian. L\'e2m Tr\u7909 , M\'e3 Thi\'ean \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i do Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca c\u7911 a c\u7853 u h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n c\u7909 c di\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tr\'e1nh kh\u7887 i li\'ean quan."\cb1 \
