\cb3 "Tr\'ec Di\'ean." H\uc0\u7855 n tr\u7847 m gi\u7885 ng g\u7885 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, "C\u7853 u d\'f9ng l\u432 \u417 ng t\'e2m n\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi quan t\'e2m c\'e1i g\'ec \u432 ? H\u7855 n kh\'f4ng h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u ngh\u297  h\u7855 n s\u7869  quan t\'e2m s\u7889 ng ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c \u432 ? H\u7855 n ch\u7881  c\u7847 n th\u7913  h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n, v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng th\'e8m b\u7853 n t\'e2m th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y s\u7869  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh c\'e1i g\'ec. \u272 \u7871 n t\'f4i c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn r\'f5 s\u7921  t\'ecnh, c\u7853 u th\u7871  n\'e0o l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7845 t th\u7901 i tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c. H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i kh\'f4ng sai, c\u7853 u th\'edch Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y m\u7895 i \u273 \'eam chung ch\u259 n chung g\u7889 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean bi\u7871 t r\'f5 t\'ednh t\'ecnh \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, c\u7853 u th\'edch h\u7855 n, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ch\u7895  n\'e0o kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u d\'f9ng l\'fd tr\'ed kh\'e1ch quan m\'e0 n\'f3i, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n b\'e1c l\u7901 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 sai.\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7855 n mu\u7889 n s\u7889 ng, mu\u7889 n \u7903  b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 ch\u7845 p ni\u7879 m c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec sai. Nh\u432 ng nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  h\u7855 n d\'f9ng \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u7841 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7909 c \u273 \'edch ph\u7843 i tr\u7843  gi\'e1 qu\'e1 l\u7899 n." Gi\u7885 ng H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y cay \u273 \u7855 ng, "M\u7897 t \'e1c linh nh\u432  v\u7853 y, H\u7913 a gia b\u7885 n t\'f4i tr\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 bi\u7879 n ph\'e1p. T\'f4i mu\u7889 n n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\u7853 u c\'f3 c\'e1ch \u273 \u7875  h\u7855 n bu\'f4ng xu\u7889 ng. \u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean, tin hay kh\'f4ng, quy\u7873 n l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n v\u7851 n \u7903  trong tay c\u7853 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng m\u7903  kh\'f3a, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7897 t th\'e2n h\u417 i l\u7841 nh \u273 \u7849 y c\u7917 a \u273 i v\'e0o. Tay tr\'e1i h\u7855 n c\u7847 m m\u7897 t t\'fai gi\u7845 y m\'e0u \u273 en, b\'ean trong \u273 \u7921 ng nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  c\u7847 n \u273 \u7875  th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n ph\'e1p tr\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m nh\'ecn th\u7845 y H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y m\u7855 t h\u7855 n h\u417 i t\u7889 i l\u7841 i, l\u7841 i nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Th\'ec ra c\'f3 kh\'e1ch t\u7899 i nh\'e0."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Nh\uc0\u432 ng h\'ecnh nh\u432  H\u7913 a c\'f4ng t\u7917  \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n thu\u7897 c v\u7873  nh\'e2n th\u7871  r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901 , \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi li\u7871 c m\u7897 t c\'e1i c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7841 , nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7869  n\'f3i th\u7859 ng ra nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u361 ng s\u7919 ng s\u7901  t\u7841 i ch\u7895 , nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "... Anh n\'f3i c\'e1i g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7853 u ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i. C\u7853 u qu\'ean r\u7891 i sao?" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, th\u7843 n nhi\'ean nh\u432  \u273 ang n\'f3i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n b\'e1c, ch\u7881  c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn tay m\'ecnh, \'e1nh m\u7855 t l\u7897  v\u7867  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tin, m\u7897 t m\'ecnh l\u7849 m b\u7849 m: "... M\'ecnh, m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec th\'eam, \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u7891  l\'ean b\'e0n, \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \'f4m eo c\u7853 u \u273 \u7847 y t\'ednh chi\u7871 m h\u7919 u n\'f3i kh\u7869 : "A Di\'ean, \u273 \'eam nay ch\'fang ta \u273 \u432 a H\u7913 a c\'f4ng t\u7917  \u273 i c\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i nh\'e9? D\u7915 ng \u7903  nh\'e2n gian \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec t\u7889 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh m\uc0\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7901 i v\u7873  ph\'eda H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y. L\'fac n\'e0y h\u7855 n d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 ch\'ecm trong h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n, m\u7897 t l\'fac l\u7841 i l\u7849 m b\u7849 m "\u272 \'fang, m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i", m\u7897 t l\'fac l\u7841 i k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng ph\u7843 n b\'e1c "Kh\'f4ng, sao c\'f3 th\u7875 , kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\'ecnh \u273 ang s\u7889 ng r\u7845 t t\u7889 t \u432 " ... Sau khi b\u7883  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7841 ch tr\u7847 n ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, h\u7855 n ho\'e0n to\'e0n ch\'ecm trong th\u7871  gi\u7899 i ri\'eang c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\u7885 i t\'ean hai l\u7847 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y v\u7851 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u7871 n khi Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ho\'e0n th\'e0nh ph\'e1p tr\u7853 n, trong l\'fac \u273 \'f3 h\u7855 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 i\'ean \u273 i\'ean kh\'f9ng kh\'f9ng m\'e0 l\u7849 m b\u7849 m "\u272 \'e3 ch\u7871 t" "C\'f2n s\u7889 ng", \'e1nh m\u7855 t nh\'ecn tr\u7915 ng tr\u7915 ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta s\u7903 n t\'f3c g\'e1y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\u7843 nh n\'e0y c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e0nh l\'f2ng, th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "\u272 \u7875  n\'f3 \u273 i c\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7887  gi\u7885 ng c\'e1o bi\u7879 t ngo\u7841 i, sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 i t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y. Nh\'ecn H\u7913 a nh\u7883  thi\u7871 u gia kh\'ed ph\'e1ch ng\'e0y x\u432 a bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh c\'e1i d\u7841 ng n\'e0y, ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n thu\u7903  nh\u7887  c\u7843  hai quen bi\u7871 t, c\u7853 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i \'fd ki\u7871 n c\u7853 u th\'eam, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c thi ph\'e1p ti\u7877 n \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i v\'e0 H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\'f9ng \u273 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn hai th\'e2n \uc0\u7843 nh quen thu\u7897 c d\u7847 n tan bi\u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t, c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'f4 l\u7921 c ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i qua c\u7853 u \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, nh\u7865  gi\u7885 ng an \u7911 i: "A Di\'ean \u273 \u7915 ng s\u7907 , c\'f2n c\'f3 ta \u7903  \u273 \'e2y." D\u7895  Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u432  khi c\'f2n nh\u7887  g\u7863 p \'e1c m\u7897 ng t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7887  gi\u7885 ng ngh\u7865 n ng\'e0o c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u d\u7921 a tr\'ean vai h\u7855 n, th\u7845 p gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "T\u7915  khi r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c, em th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  r\u7857 ng khi g\u7863 p l\u7841 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7889 ng n\u7919 a. Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\'fai \u7849 n r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c b\u7883  sao v\u7853 y? L\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c anh v\u7897 i v\'e0ng tr\u7903  v\u7873  l\'e0 v\'ec sao?" C\u7853 u g\u7885 i h\u7855 n l\'e0 Ngh\'eanh Chi, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca mang \u273 \u7847 y s\u7921  \u7927  l\u7841 i nh\u432  khi c\'f2n nh\u7887  m\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh g\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi vu\u7889 t l\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i c\'e2u cu\u7889 i, ch\u7881  n\'f3i: "Thi\'ean s\u432  ba nh\'e0 H\u7913 a, Di\u7879 p, Tr\'ec truy\u7873 n th\u7915 a nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m kh\'f4ng \'edt chuy\u7879 n t\'e0 \'e1m kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i bi\u7871 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  qu\u7927  bi\u7871 t, t\'edch t\u7909  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c s\u7869  b\u7897 c ph\'e1t ra, l\'fac n\'e0y ch\'ednh l\'e0 gieo gi\'f3 g\u7863 t b\'e3o. N\u417 i \u273 \'f3 qu\u7927  kh\'ed qu\'e1 n\u7863 ng, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng tr\'e1nh kh\u7887 i. B\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 v\'e3ng sinh r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n nh\u7899  l\u7841 i n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, do d\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng n\'f3i: "H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y v\u7915 a r\u7891 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y n\'f3i v\u7899 i em l\'e0 anh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, c\'f2n n\'f3i b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897  c\u7911 a anh n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn c\u7853 u kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i: "A Di\'ean ho\'e0i nghi ta \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3, ch\u7881  l\'e0... h\u417 i lo l\u7855 ng, c\u361 ng c\'f3 s\u7907  h\'e3i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y b\u7883  \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng b\u7903 i m\'ea ch\u432 \u7899 ng c\u7911 a qu\u7927  kh\'ed, \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng ph\'e2n bi\u7879 t n\u7893 i, ngay c\u7843  m\'ecnh s\u7889 ng hay ch\u7871 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899 , l\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 \u7875  trong l\'f2ng." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, d\u7855 t c\u7853 u tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 , "Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ca ca v\u7851 n \u273 ang \u7903  \u273 \'e2y \u432 , n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \'eam qua ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng em c\u7843  \u273 \'eam l\'e0 ai? C\'f2n ph\u7843 i ch\u7913 ng minh v\u7899 i em th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \'e2y, ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i." N\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 o\u7841 n sau, ng\u7919  kh\'ed h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 th\'eam v\'e0i ph\u7847 n \'e1i mu\u7897 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\u7845 y l\'f2ng m\'e0 h\'f4n kh\'f3e m\'f4i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, m\u7903  to m\u7855 t nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i m\u7873 m xu\u7889 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t h\u7871 t ph\'f2ng b\u7883 , nh\u432  con trai kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7873  ph\'f2ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n m\u7903  v\u7887  ra, \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  ph\u7847 n th\u7883 t m\u7873 m, h\u7845 p d\u7851 n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7855 t n\'f3 n\'e2ng trong tay, t\'f9y \'fd vu\u7889 t ve th\u7883 t trai m\u7873 m m\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn d\'e1ng v\u7867  n\'e0y c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t s\'e2u \u273 en tr\'e0n \u273 \u7847 y th\u7887 a m\'e3n, th\u7903  d\'e0i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng. Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f2ng hai tay l\'ean c\u7893  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng, y\'ean t\u297 nh m\'e0 nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i. \'d4ng ngo\u7841 i c\'f9ng H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y v\u7915 a \u273 i, c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\'e2m t\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  c\u7847 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi mu\u7889 n, c\u7853 u s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\u7921  tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng th\'e2n thi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n ti\u7871 ng h\'e1t cao v\'fat, gi\u7885 ng nam kh\'e0n \'c2u M\u297  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c khi\u7871 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7915 ng t\u7881 nh. C\u7853 u m\u7903  m\u7855 t, tay h\u417 i d\'f9ng s\u7913 c \u273 \u7849 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ra, ra kh\u7887 i ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  \u273 i xem th\u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t chi\u7871 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\'e0u x\'e1m b\u7841 c \u273 ang rung tr\'ean b\'e0n, gi\u7885 ng h\'e1t vang ra t\u7915  n\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0 \uc0\u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ti\u7877 n h\u7855 n \u273 i nh\u432 ng gi\u7919  l\u7841 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i qua, m\'e0n h\'ecnh hi\u7879 n "Ti\u7875 u H\'e2n". C\u7853 u d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat, m\u7903  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\u7855 t m\'e1y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng h\'e1t nam l\u7853 p t\u7913 c im b\u7863 t, trong loa truy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7885 ng n\u7919  quen thu\u7897 c. Nghe ra Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7853 n m\'e1y, H\u7913 a H\'e2n ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean? Sao l\u7841 i l\'e0 c\u7853 u, anh t\'f4i \u273 \'e2u?"\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'f5 r\'e0ng tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng l\'e2u H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\'f2n ng\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y nh\u7855 n tin cho H\u7913 a H\'e2n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i ngh\u7865 n l\u7901 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean gi\u7843 i th\'edch v\u7899 i H\u7913 a H\'e2n r\u7857 ng H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, r\u7857 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7855 n tin b\u7843 o c\'f4 r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i H\u7913 a gia \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a H\'e2n th\u7845 y c\u7853 u im l\u7863 ng c\u361 ng nh\u432  nh\u7853 n ra \u273 i\u7873 u g\'ec \u273 \'f3, tr\u7847 m m\u7863 c m\u7897 t l\'e1t, n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec, c\u7853 u n\'f3i \u273 i, x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec?" Gi\u7885 ng c\'f4 r\u7845 t tr\u7845 n t\u297 nh, ch\u7881  l\'e0 h\'f4 h\u7845 p h\u417 i nhanh.\cb1 \
