\cb3 "Xin l\uc0\u7895 i \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  c\u7853 u g\u7863 p H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\u7847 n cu\u7889 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng sao, c\'e1m \uc0\u417 n c\u7853 u, t\'f4i hi\u7875 u m\'e0, \u273 \u7875  anh t\'f4i su\'f4n s\u7867  s\u7899 m r\u7901 i \u273 i m\u7899 i l\'e0 t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t." Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe ra gi\u7885 ng H\u7913 a H\'e2n ngh\'e8n ngh\u7865 n, "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng sao, kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n lo cho t\'f4i \u273 \'e2u, t\'f4i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i l\u7841 i im l\u7863 ng, qua h\u417 n m\u7897 t ph\'fat H\u7913 a H\'e2n m\u7899 i l\u7841 i m\u7903  mi\u7879 ng: "C\'f2n m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c t\'f4i mu\u7889 n nh\u7901  c\u7853 u, khi n\'e0o s\u7921  t\'ecnh \u7903  n\'fai \u7849 n b\'ean kia gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t xong c\u7853 u nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh ph\u7843 i n\'f3i cho t\'f4i bi\u7871 t. T\'f4i ph\u7843 i tr\u7903  v\u7873 , tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\u7853 n x\'e1c anh t\'f4i." V\u7899 i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i \u7903  \u273 \'f3, m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\'f4 ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  quay v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i an \u7911 i c\'f4 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, ch\u7881  nghi\'eam t\'fac \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, t\'e2m t\'ecnh n\u7863 ng n\u7873  c\'fap \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i.\cb1 \
