\f1\i0 \cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 Chu Ngh\uc0\u297  nghe n\'f3i \u273 \u7897 ng l\'f2ng, b\'e8n th\u432 \u7907 ng bi\u7875 u l\'ean Nguy\'ean \u272 \u7871  r\u7857 ng V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o v\'f4 t\u7897 i. Tuy nhi\'ean V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t vi\u7879 c n\'e0y, m\'e0 trong l\'fac y\u7871 n ti\u7879 c \u7903  ph\u7911  Chu ngh\u297 , nghe Ng\'f4i n\'f3i v\u7873  vi\u7879 c di\u7879 t gi\u7863 c, t\u432 \u7903 ng r\u7857 ng mu\u7889 n \'e1m ch\u7881  m\'ecnh, n\'ean \'f4ng o\'e1n h\u7853 n Ngh\u297 .
\f1\i0 \cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng T\u7845 n Nguy\'ean \u272 \u7871  kh\'f4ng truy c\u7913 u V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o, l\u7841 i phong cho \'f4ng l\'e0m Ti\u7873 n phong \u272 \u7841 i \u273 \'f4 \u273 \u7889 c, c\'f9ng \u272 \u7899 i Uy\'ean l\'e0m Phi\'eau k\u7883  t\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e2n \u273 \u7875  c\'f9ng ch\u7889 ng V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \'f4n v\'e0o th\'e1ng 3 n\u259 m 322.[16], tuy nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ch\u7889 ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o c\'f9ng \u272 i\'eau Hi\u7879 p, L\u432 u Ng\'f4i, \u272 \u7899 i Uy\'ean, Chu Ngh\u297 , Qu\'e1ch D\u7853 t v\'e0 Ngu \u272 \'e0m b\u7883  V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \'f4n \u273 \'e1nh b\u7841 i. V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \'f4n sau \u273 \'f3 nhanh ch\'f3ng k\'e9o binh v\u7873  Ki\u7871 n Khang, n\u7855 m gi\u7919  tri\u7873 u \u273 \'ecnh, t\u7921  x\u432 ng l\'e0m Th\u7915 a t\u432 \u7899 ng, l\u7841 i phong cho V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o l\'e0m Th\u432 \u7907 ng th\u432  l\u7879 nh. V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \'f4n l\u7841 i c\'f3 \'fd l\u7853 t \u273 \u7893  Nguy\'ean \u272 \u7871  \u273 \u7875  l\'ean ng\'f4i nh\u432 ng V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o t\u7915  ch\u7889 i, l\u7845 y l\'fd l\u7869  ra \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \'e1p l\'e0m V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \'f4n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.
