\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn \uc0\u7843 nh ch\u7909 p trong tay s\u7919 ng s\u7901  t\u7841 i ch\u7895 . \u272 \'e2y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 th\u7871  n\'e0o, Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca v\'ec sao ph\u7843 i l\u7853 p m\u7897  cho ch\'ednh m\'ecnh, c\'f2n t\u7921  m\'ecnh vi\u7871 t t\'ean l\'ean bia m\u7897 .\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t b\'f3ng \u273 en ph\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n, nam nh\'e2n im l\u7863 ng kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n, th\'e2n m\u7853 t \'f4m eo c\u7853 u, gh\'e9 v\'e0o tai c\u7853 u d\u7883 u d\'e0ng n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean \u273 ang xem g\'ec th\u7871 ? Sao l\u7841 i \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ho\uc0\u7843 ng s\u7907 , v\u7897 i v\'e0ng v\'f4 th\u7913 c t\u7855 t m\'e0n h\'ecnh, n\u7855 m di \u273 \u7897 ng trong tay quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ng\u7851 m ngh\u297  m\u7897 t l\'e1t, l\u7841 i c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i m\u7903  t\u7845 m \u7843 nh v\u7915 a nh\'ecn th\u7845 y cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi xem: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, t\u7841 i sao anh ph\u7843 i l\u7853 p bia m\u7897  cho ch\'ednh m\'ecnh?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi hai tay \'f4m v\'f2ng quanh c\u7853 u, th\u7901  \u417  nh\'ecn \u7843 nh ch\u7909 p nh\u432  \u273 ang nh\'ecn bi\u7875 n b\'e1o giao th\'f4ng b\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i bia m\u7897  ghi t\'ean m\'ecnh. H\u7855 n thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i: "Con ch\'e1u Di\u7879 p gia c\'f3 truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng t\u7921  x\'e2y m\u7897  l\u7853 p bia t\u7915  s\u7899 m, l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7897  th\u7843 n nhi\'ean tho\u7843 i m\'e1i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i khi\u7871 n ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 v\u7867  kinh ng\u7841 c th\'e1i qu\'e1. Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\u417 i do d\u7921 , n\'f3i ti\u7871 p: "H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i \u273 \'e0o m\u7897  anh ch\'ednh l\'e0 c\'e1i n\'e0y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "Kh\'f4ng sai. L\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c ta tr\u7903  v\u7873  c\u361 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec vi\u7879 c n\'e0y, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'e1o m\u7897 t nh\'f3m ng\u432 \u7901 i H\u7913 a gia \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean v\'f4 c\u7899  l\u7867 n v\'e0o c\u7845 m \u273 \u7883 a Di\u7879 p gia \u273 \'e0o m\u7897  c\u7911 a ta, cho n\'ean ta m\u7899 i quay v\u7873  ng\u259 n c\u7843 n."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe h\uc0\u7855 n n\'f3i v\u7853 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean l\u7841 i sinh ra m\u7897 t nghi ho\u7863 c: "N\'fai \u7849 n b\'ean kia v\u7851 n c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p gia \u432 ... H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i ng\u432 \u7901 i H\u7913 a gia \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, v\u7853 y ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p gia th\'ec sao? Ng\u432 \u7901 i truy\u7873 n tin cho ca ca th\'ec sao?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nhu h\'f2a nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, n\'f3i kh\u7869 : "\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4 h\uc0\u7845 p Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ng\u432 ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7845 y c\u7853 u ng\'e2y ng\u432 \u7901 i, h\'f4n l\'ean m\u7855 t c\u7853 u tr\u7845 n an: "B\u7885 n h\u7885  ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, c\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c 'S\u7889 ng' nh\u432  v\u7853 y, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t." Gi\u7885 ng h\u7855 n nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng b\'e2ng qu\u417  nh\u432  \u273 ang n\'f3i m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng quan tr\u7885 ng r\u7845 t kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, ng\u417  ng\'e1c m\u7863 c cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi d\u7855 t m\'ecnh tr\u7903  v\u7873  ph\'f2ng ng\u7911 . L\'fac r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia, c\u7853 u c\'f2n \u273 ang suy ngh\u297  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca s\u7869  gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t t\'ecnh h\'ecnh n\u417 i \u273 \'f3 nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t h\u7855 n c\'f3 c\'e1ch g\'ec kh\'f4ng, \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  c\u7853 u m\u7899 i hi\u7875 u ra, \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i t\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7843 o ng\u432 \u7907 c \u7903  n\'fai \u7849 n kia h\u7855 n v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh gi\u7843 i quy\u7871 t, ho\'e0n to\'e0n m\u7863 c cho m\u7885 i th\u7913  ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, b\'e0n tay Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7855 m c\u7853 u, l\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y. So v\u7899 i tay Tr\'ec Dung l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c k\'e9o c\u7853 u, tay H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y c\u7847 m ch\u7863 t tay c\u7853 u c\'f2n l\u7841 nh h\u417 n, l\u7841 nh \u273 \u7871 n th\u7845 u x\u432 \u417 ng. Ch\u7881  l\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra. C\u7853 u ch\u7881  \u273 au l\'f2ng s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, mu\u7889 n d\'f9ng c\u417  th\u7875  m\'ecnh \u7911  \u7845 m cho h\u7855 n. Cho d\'f9 t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c th\'e2n m\u7853 t nh\u7845 t hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'e1c th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7903 i t\u7845 t gi\'e0y cho c\u7853 u, \'f4m c\u7853 u n\u7857 m tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n t\u7881  m\u7881  h\'f4n m\'e1 h\'f4n m\'f4i c\u7853 u. Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7909  n\u7909  h\'f4n l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o m\'e0 d\u7883 u d\'e0ng, l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \'fd ni\u7879 m tr\'e1nh n\'e9 n\u7893 i l\'ean trong \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Dung, cha, \'f4ng ngo\uc0\u7841 i, H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y... G\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t t\u7915 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i hi\u7879 n l\'ean tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t c\u7853 u. Tr\'ec Dung n\'f3i "\u272 \u7915 ng tin Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, \u273 \u7915 ng v\'ec h\u7855 n m\'e0 \u7903  l\u7841 i"; cha tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac \u273 i, ra s\u7913 c xua tay v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\'e1nh xa Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi; \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i n\'f3i "Ngo\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n kia c\u7911 a con l\'e0 h\'ecnh d\u7841 ng g\'ec, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y xung quanh h\u7855 n to\'e0n qu\u7927  kh\'ed v\'e0 \'e2m kh\'ed" ; H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y, m\u7897 t \'e2m h\u7891 n l\u7841 i t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y n\'f3i cho c\u7853 u hay "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t" ... V\'ec sao t\u7845 t c\u7843  b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7873 u mu\u7889 n c\u7853 u r\u7901 i xa Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. M\'e0 cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u ch\u7871 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n nh\u7845 t b\'ean c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, gi\u7901  ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng b\'ean g\u7889 i n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean si\uc0\u7871 t ch\u259 n nh\u7855 m ch\u7863 t hai m\u7855 t, c\u7893  h\u7885 ng ph\'e1t ra ti\u7871 ng ngh\'e8n ngh\u7865 n nh\u7887 , kh\u7893  s\u7903  m\'e0 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao. C\u7853 u ch\u7907 t ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, b\u7843 n th\'e2n b\'e2y gi\u7901  ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c tin t\u432 \u7903 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'e1c. Ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0y, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f2n g\'ec n\u432 \u771 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang r\u7891 i, v\u7851 n c\'f2n gia \u273 \'ecnh T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m. C\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f2n m\u7897 t b\u7857 ng h\u7919 u c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f9ng v\'e0o sinh ra t\u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghe th\u7845 y c\u7853 u ngh\u7865 n ng\'e0o, ph\u7911  \u7903  ph\'eda tr\'ean c\u7849 n th\u7853 n h\'f4n hai m\u7855 t nh\u7855 m ch\u7863 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, ki\'ean nh\u7851 n an \u7911 i: "A Di\'ean \u273 \u7915 ng kh\u7893  s\u7903 , ca ca v\u7851 n b\'ean em m\'e0, ca ca s\u7869  lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean em, ngoan."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qua m\uc0\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i r\u7847 u r\u297  "V\'e2ng" r\u7891 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, m\u7903  m\u7855 t \'f4m ch\u7863 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'e1n l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ngh\'eanh Chi." C\uc0\u7853 u lo s\u7907  kh\'f4ng y\'ean m\'e0 g\u7885 i t\'ean h\u7855 n, ch\'f4n m\u7863 t v\'e0o c\u7893  \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng kh\u7869  c\u7885 , "Anh \u273 \u7915 ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n em... \u272 \u7915 ng g\u7841 t em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Qua v\'e0i gi\'e2y Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7899 i l\'ean ti\u7871 ng, h\'e0ng mi d\'e0i r\u361  xu\u7889 ng, che khu\u7845 t \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en: "S\u7869  kh\'f4ng kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n em." H\u7855 n k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean ra kh\u7887 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, \'e1p xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i th\'e2n c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u d\'f9ng ch\'f3p m\u361 i ch\u7841 m ch\'f3p m\u361 i c\u7853 u, kh\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "H\u417 n n\u7919 a, ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i, ca ca c\'f3 l\'fac n\'e0o l\u7915 a g\u7841 t em?"\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4 h\uc0\u7845 p giao tri\u7873 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\u7869  "V\'e2ng..." m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, \'f4m h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec, m\u7897 t l\'e1t sau duy tr\'ec t\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y ng\u7911  m\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7903  m\'ecnh n\u7857 m qua b\'ean tr\'e1i, ch\u7889 ng m\u7897 t b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, \u273 \u432 a tay nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng vu\u7889 t ve hai m\'e1 v\'e0 ch\'f3p m\u361 i, kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng \u273 \'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 \'fd c\u432 \u7901 i v\'f4 c\'f9ng nhu h\'f2a. Tr\'ec Di\'ean trong gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng b\u7855 t l\u7845 y b\'e0n tay l\'e0m lo\u7841 n c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, h\u7855 n li\u7873 n th\u7915 a c\u417  n\u7855 m ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nghi\'eang th\'e2n h\'f4n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang ng\u7911  say, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\u7881  non: "Ti\u7875 u b\u7843 o b\u7889 i, ta y\'eau em nh\u7845 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Kh\'f4ng, " h\uc0\u7855 n c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, k\'e9o to\'e0n b\u7897  ng\u432 \u7901 i \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, "Ch\u7881  y\'eau m\'ecnh em."\cb1 \
\cb3 \'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng xem nh\u432  tr\u7903  l\u7841 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng m\u7885 i khi c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Ch\u7911  qu\'e1n \u273 \u7849 y xe b\'e1n qu\'e0 v\u7863 t \u273 \u7891  \u259 n s\'e1ng than v\u7899 i kh\'e1ch quen tr\u7913 ng g\'e0 l\u7841 i t\u259 ng gi\'e1, b\'e0 ch\u7911  ti\u7879 m \u259 n d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u v\u7899 i d\'ec b\'e1n h\'e0ng tr\'e1i c\'e2y b\'ean c\u7841 nh o\'e1n tr\'e1ch th\u7847 y gi\'e1o l\u7841 i g\u7885 i ph\u7909  huynh, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y sau gi\u7901  tan h\u7885 c tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7841 i th\u7845 y h\u7885 c sinh \u7847 m \u297  c\'e3i nhau, c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f9a vui v\u7867 ... M\u7895 i ng\'e0y tr\'f4i qua \u273 \u7873 u gi\u7889 ng l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t \u273 \'f4i t\'ecnh nh\'e2n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y c\'f9ng \u259 n c\'f9ng ng\u7911 , th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng c\'f9ng nhau \u273 i du l\u7883 ch, cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng r\u7845 t m\'e3n nguy\u7879 n. N\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c vi\u7879 c, \u273 \u7871 n th\'e1ng ch\'edn m\u7899 i v\'e0o ch\'ednh th\u7913 c n\'ean kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian n\'e0y tr\u7903  n\'ean v\'f4 c\'f9ng nh\'e0n r\u7895 i, ngo\'e0i vi\u7879 c c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y nhau th\'ec th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng g\u7885 i cho T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m h\u7887 i han t\'ecnh h\'ecnh c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a h\u7855 n, h\u7887 i th\u259 m s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean v\'e0 \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\'e0 \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 b\u7841 n h\u7885 c, quan h\u7879  r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, c\'f3 \u273 \'f4i khi g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i t\u7899 i, \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean nghe ra l\'e0 c\u7853 u li\u7873 n gi\'e0nh \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i o\'e1n tr\'e1ch n\u7917 a ng\'e0y v\u7899 i c\u7853 u r\u7857 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m ch\u7881  ch\u259 m ch\u259 m c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c, kh\'f4ng th\'e8m quan t\'e2m \u273 \u7871 n hai m\u7865  con, nh\u432 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f4 kh\'f4ng th\u7853 t s\u7921  tr\'e1ch ch\u7891 ng bao nhi\'eau, Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u432 \u7901 ng nghe r\u7891 i c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7899 n, th\u7853 m ch\'ed h\u7865 n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i sau khi sinh b\'e9 xong s\u7869  nh\u7853 n l\'e0m cha nu\'f4i c\u7911 a \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7901  c\u7853 u n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i xong, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi v\u7867  m\u7863 t \u273 \'e3 b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  l\u7841 i dung t\'fang nh\'ecn c\u7853 u: "Em gi\u7887 i l\u7855 m, kh\'f4ng th\'e8m n\'f3i tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e3 nh\u7853 n con nu\'f4i cho ta r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7889 n mu\u7889 n ph\u7843 n b\'e1c, nh\u432 ng ngh\u297  l\u7841 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n nh\u7853 n con nu\'f4i, v\u7853 y ch\u7859 ng ph\u7843 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng s\u7869  l\'e0m cha nu\'f4i hay sao? Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\'f3i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng sai. C\u7853 u \u273 \'e0nh \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t r\u7847 m r\'ec ng\u7891 i qua m\u7897 t b\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\u7899 i h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i gian c\'f2n l\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghi\'ean c\u7913 u cu\u7889 n b\'fat k\'fd Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u432 a cho m\'ecnh, trong b\'fat k\'fd ghi ch\'e9p r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n l\u7841 i h\u7919 u d\u7909 ng, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7853 t \u273 \u7871 n ph\u7847 n sau th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p t\'e1c d\u7909 ng r\u7845 t gi\u7889 ng th\u7913  trong mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia d\'f9ng cho c\u7853 u, \u273 \u7873 u c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y hai gi\u7899 i \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng, th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e2m h\u7891 n qu\u7927  kh\'ed. Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7917  d\'f9ng thu\u7853 t n\'e0y v\u7899 i ch\'ednh m\'ecnh, c\'f3 th\u7875  b\u7903 i v\'ec tu vi c\u7911 a c\u7853 u ch\u432 a t\u7899 i n\u417 i m\'e0 thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i cao s\'e2u n\'ean c\u7853 u th\u7917  m\u7845 y l\u7847 n \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 hi\u7879 u qu\u7843 . Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ki\'ean tr\'ec n\u7919 a, l\u7853 t ti\u7871 p xem nh\u7919 ng n\u7897 i dung ph\'eda sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\u7841 i qua n\u7917 a th\'e1ng, th\u7901 i ti\u7871 t n\'f3ng d\u7847 n l\'ean t\u7915 ng ng\'e0y, bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng th\'edch d\'ednh l\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7911  b\u7903 i v\'ec m\'e1t, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng t\'f9y \'fd c\u7853 u. T\'ecnh tr\u7841 ng c\u417  th\u7875  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng t\u7889 t, theo l\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i l\'e0 v\u7851 n lu\'f4n u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c n\'ean ki\u7875 m so\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i t\u7889 t, l\u7847 n tr\u7903  v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 nh\'e2n ti\u7879 n th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t ti\u7875 u ph\u7851 u, gi\u7843 i ph\u7851 u thu\u7853 n l\u7907 i th\'e0nh c\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i chi\u7873 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u7903  nh\'e0 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, n\u7857 m thi\'eam thi\u7871 p tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7917 a m\'ea n\u7917 a t\u7881 nh. Sau khi \u259 n tr\u432 a xong Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'f3 h\u7913 ng khi d\u7877  c\u7853 u m\u7897 t h\u7891 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  h\u7855 n gi\'e0y v\'f2 kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, kh\'f3c l\'f3c n\'f3i bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i mu\u7889 n \u259 n canh c\'e1, cho n\'ean ch\u7881 nh \u273 \u7889 n \u273 \u7855 p ch\u259 n cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean xong Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i mua c\'e1, ch\u7881  c\'f2n Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7897 t m\'ecnh n\u7857 m ngh\u7881  trong ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong ph\'f2ng h\uc0\u417 i oi b\u7913 c, b\'ean ngo\'e0i tr\u7901 i \'e2m u, h\'ecnh nh\u432  s\u7855 p m\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean chui trong ch\uc0\u259 n bu\u7891 n b\u7921 c \u273 \u7871 n h\u417 i kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u, x\u7889 c ch\u259 n l\'ean nh\'ecn th\u7845 y d\u7845 u v\u7871 t tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh, m\u7871 u m\'e1o qu\u417  \'e1o ng\u7911  m\u7863 c v\'e0o, xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i ra ban c\'f4ng m\u7903  c\u7917 a, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 gi\'f3 th\u7893 i v\'e0o m\u7899 i tr\u7903  l\u7841 i l\u259 n l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng. V\u7915 a r\u7891 i ra qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u m\u7891  h\'f4i, c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m m\u7903  \u273 i\u7873 u h\'f2a. L\'fac chui v\'e0o trong ch\u259 n m\u417  m\'e0ng s\u7855 p ng\u7911  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f2n \'e2m th\u7847 m ph\u7881  nh\u7893  b\u7843 n th\'e2n tr\'f4i qua m\u7895 i ng\'e0y th\u7871  n\'e0y qu\u7843  th\u7921 c qu\'e1 sa \u273 \u7885 a qu\'e1 kh\'f4ng ti\u7871 n b\u7897 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t qua bao l\'e2u, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng tr\'f4i qua l\u7841 i c\u361 ng nh\u432  ch\u7881  m\u7899 i ch\u7899 p m\u7855 t, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'f9i trong ch\u259 n, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng l\u7841 nh, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  c\'f3 m\u7897 t th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 r\u7845 t l\u7841 nh \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u. C\u7853 u d\u7847 n d\u7847 n thanh t\u7881 nh, r\u7845 t nhanh \'fd th\u7913 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u7843 o gi\'e1c, th\u7921 c s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng c\u7841 nh gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh, c\'f2n g\u7885 i t\'ean m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean, Tr\'ec Di\'ean..." Khe kh\uc0\u7869  nh\u432  s\u7907  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i ta ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\'e3nh li\uc0\u7879 t m\u7903  m\u7855 t, nh\'ecn v\u7873  ph\'eda ph\'e1t ra \'e2m thanh, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c th\u7845 y T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng cu\u7889 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng, d\'e1ng v\u7867  nh\u432  m\u7885 i khi nh\u432 ng c\'f3 ch\'fat kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng. C\'f3 ch\'fat qu\'e1i d\u7883 , nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0 \u273 i\u7875 m g\'ec b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\u7843  kinh nghi ho\u7863 c ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, nh\'ecn b\u7841 n m\'ecnh b\u7845 t ch\u7907 t \u273 \u7871 n th\u259 m: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng? Sao c\u7853 u l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y? V\'e0o b\u7857 ng c\'e1ch n\'e0o? Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng kh\'f3a c\u7917 a \u432 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , t\'f4i t\u7899 i \u273 \u7875  c\'e1o bi\u7879 t c\u7853 u. Quy\'ean Quy\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean c\u7853 u c\u7913  gi\u7845 u c\'f4 \u7845 y \u273 i, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi sinh xong kh\u7887 e l\u7841 i r\u7891 i h\u7861 ng n\'f3i cho c\'f4 \u7845 y bi\u7871 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ph\'e1t gi\'e1c kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \'fang, cau m\'e0y nh\'ecn h\u7855 n n\'f3i l\u7899 n: "\u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 l\'e0m sao? C\u7853 u n\'f3i v\u7853 y l\'e0 c\'f3 \'fd g\'ec?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  th\u7845 y T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m nh\'ecn th\u7859 ng c\u7853 u: "Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , t\'f4i ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i, tu\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac c\u7853 u g\u7885 i t\u7899 i t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
