\f1\b0 \cf2 "... \uc0\u272 \'e3 ch\u7871 t?" Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7875  tin m\'e0 nh\'ecn h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean g\uc0\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t c\u7913 ng \u273 \u7901  c\u7911 a T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u7889  n\u7863 n ra m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7893 : "Kh\'f4ng sai, t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t r\u7891 i, nh\u432 ng t\'f4i l\u7841 i qu\'ean m\u7845 t cho n\'ean v\u7851 n \u7903  c\'f9ng m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia... Nh\u432 ng h\'f4m nay l\'fac...t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i, t\'f4i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n tay m\'ecnh \u273 ang \u273 \'e8 tr\'ean c\u7893  Quy\'ean Quy\'ean... T\'f4i \u273 \'e3 su\'fdt gi\u7871 t ch\u7871 t c\'f4 \u7845 y." N\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y h\u7855 n c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, nh\'ecn hai tay c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, \u273 \'f4i b\'e0n tay d\'e0y r\u7897 ng \u273 \'e1ng tin c\u7853 y v\u7851 n \u273 ang kh\u7869  run.\cb1 \
\cb3 "C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  ma \'e1m, t\'f4i r\u7845 t s\u7907  h\'e3i, v\u7897 i v\'e3 ch\u7841 y ra kh\u7887 i nh\'e0, sau \u273 \'f3 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c t\'f4i nh\u7899  ra r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 ang \u273 i\u7873 u tra v\u7909  \'e1n b\u7883  \'e1c qu\u7927  \u7849 n n\'e1u g\u7847 n thi th\u7875  n\u7841 n nh\'e2n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t." H\u7855 n th\u7889 ng kh\u7893  \'f4m \u273 \u7847 u, "T\'f4i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean s\uc0\u7919 ng s\u7901  nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, theo l\u7901 i h\u259 \u769 n n\'f3i, t\u7915 ng lu\u7891 ng kh\'ed \u273 en xen l\u7851 n m\'e0u m\'e1u t\u432 \u417 i t\'faa ra t\u7915  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, m\u7855 t h\u7855 n c\u361 ng tr\u7903  n\'ean \u273 \u7887  qu\u7841 ch. Ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  qu\u7927  h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t, th\'f4ng th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \u7897 t t\u7917  m\'e0 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh o\'e1n qu\u7927  ho\u7863 c \'e1c qu\u7927 , sau \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 \u273 i h\u7841 i ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh. T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m n\'f3i kh\'f4ng sai, "H\u7855 n" \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh o\'e1n qu\u7927 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "T\'f4i kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t ph\u7843 i l\'e0m g\'ec, t\'f4i s\u7907  t\'f4i kh\'f4ng kh\u7889 ng ch\u7871  n\u7893 i b\u7843 n th\'e2n l\u7841 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  h\u7841 i Quy\'ean Quy\'ean v\'e0 con n\'ean b\'e8n nu\u7889 t l\'e1 ph\'f9 c\u7853 u cho l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c. B\'e2y gi\u7901  t\'f4i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'ed l\u7921 c tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng y\u7871 u, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 t\'f4i s\u7855 p \u273 i r\u7891 i. Th\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , gi\u7901  t\'f4i coi nh\u432  l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i anh em \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, sau c\'f9ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t y\'eau c\u7847 u qu\'e1 \u273 \'e1ng, xin nh\u7901  c\u7853 y c\u7853 u ch\u259 m s\'f3c Quy\'ean Quy\'ean v\'e0 \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9 gi\'fap t\'f4i." T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m n\'f3i xong to\'e0n th\'e2n tr\u7903  n\'ean c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng nh\u7841 t, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng h\'f3a th\'e0nh m\u7897 t l\'e0n kh\'f3i \u273 en mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i. L\'e0n kh\'f3i h\u432 \u7899 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\'e1i l\u7841 y, sau \u273 \'f3 d\u7847 n tan bi\u7871 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c r\'e9t l\u7841 nh trong ph\'f2ng theo \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng ti\'eau t\'e1n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, s\u7901  l\'ean h\u7889 c m\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 \u432 \u7899 t, che m\u7863 t m\u7855 ng: "X\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n t\u7841 i sao kh\'f4ng t\u7899 i t\'ecm t\'f4i ch\u7913 , c\u7853 u l\'e0m v\u7853 y, ch\'ednh l\'e0 h\u7891 n phi ph\'e1ch t\'e1n r\u7891 i..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\'f3 m\u7855 ng n\u7919 a c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng thay \u273 \u7893 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec, T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\'e0 tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c t\'f4i nh\u7899  ra r\u7857 ng t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 ang \u273 i\u7873 u tra v\u7909  \'e1n b\u7883  \'e1c qu\u7927  \u7849 n n\'e1u g\u7847 n thi th\u7875  n\u7841 n nh\'e2n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Th\uc0\u432 \u7899 c K\u7867 , c\u7853 u n\'f3i c\'f3 xem c\'f3 l\u7841  kh\'f4ng, b\u7885 n t\'f4i v\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t v\u7909  \'e1n m\u7845 t t\'edch, ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'e1o \'e1n l\'e0 v\u7907  c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7845 t t\'edch, c\'f4 \u7845 y n\'f3i ch\u7891 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 t t\'edch hai ng\'e0y, t\'ecm th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y. Cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\u7885 n t\'f4i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c thi th\u7875  ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  h\u7841 i \u7903  m\u7897 t nh\'e0 tr\u7885 , c\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o k\u7871 t qu\u7843  ki\'ea\u777 m tra thi th\'ea\u777 , ch\u7891 ng c\u7911 a c\'f4 \u7845 y \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  gi\u7871 t b\u7843 y ng\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng l\u7901 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m t\u7915 ng n\'f3i quanh qu\u7849 n trong \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean. C\u7853 u v\u7897 i v\'e0ng xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7885 t t\u7899 i tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n \u273 \u7885 c s\'e1ch c\u7847 m cu\u7889 n b\'fat k\'fd c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nhanh ch\'f3ng l\u7853 t ra xem.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o l\u7901 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \u7875  ph\'e1n \u273 o\'e1n, h\u7855 n ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n gi\u7889 ng \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia v\'e0 n\'fai \u7849 n, th\u7871  nh\u432 ng th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i khu v\u7921 c nh\u7887  b\u7883  phong b\u7871  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, l\'e0m sao c\'f3 th\u7875  ph\'e1t sinh chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y? C\u7853 u kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7875  \u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng ch\u7871 t v\'f4 \'edch, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c th\u7901  \u417  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m g\'ec. C\u7853 u ph\u7843 i \u273 i nh\'ecn, nh\'ecn cho r\'f5 th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y, n\u417 i c\u7853 u \u273 ang s\u7889 ng n\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh c\'e1i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\uc0\u7845 t nhanh l\u7853 t \u273 \u7871 n thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y hai gi\u7899 i \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng. L\u7847 n n\'e0y trong l\'fac t\'e2m t\'ecnh k\'edch \u273 \u7897 ng, sau khi th\u7921 c hi\u7879 n thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p c\u7853 u ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y hai m\u7855 t h\u417 i n\'f3ng v\'e0 s\u432 ng \u273 au, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \'eam \u7903  mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'f3ng v\'e0 \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n r\u7845 t nhanh bi\u7871 n m\u7845 t, sau khi m\u7903  m\u7855 t ra, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y m\u7897 t th\u7871  gi\u7899 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7927  kh\'ed m\'e0u \u273 en d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c, c\'f2n d\'e0y h\u417 n th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia g\u7845 p tr\u259 m l\u7847 n l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 ang b\u7889 c l\'ean v\u7847 n v\u361  tr\'ean kh\'f4ng, kh\u7855 p kh\'f4ng trung kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ch\'fat \'e1nh s\'e1ng n\'e0o, t\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i t\u7847 m m\u7855 t c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn t\u7899 i \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  qu\u7927  kh\'ed m\'e0u \u273 en bao ph\u7911 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean gh\'e9 v\'e0o ban c\'f4ng nh\'ecn xu\uc0\u7889 ng ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i, trong bi\u7875 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \'f9n \'f9n nh\u432  th\u7911 y tri\u7873 u, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u361 ng c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t tr\u7855 ng to\'e1t kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\'f3ng. T\u7845 t c\u7843  b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c v\u7899 i ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh xung quanh.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7851 n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tin, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng thay qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7847 m ch\'eca kh\'f3a ch\u7841 y ra kh\u7887 i nh\'e0. \u272 i tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \u7913 ng gi\u7919 a r\u7915 ng c\'e2y trong th\'e0nh ph\u7889  hi\u7879 n \u273 \u7841 i nh\'ecn l\'ean kh\'f4ng trung \u273 en ngh\u7883 t, lo\u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c thi\u7871 u sinh kh\'ed m\'e0 v\'f4 v\u7885 ng n\'e0y l\u7841 i c\'e0ng r\'f5 th\'eam m\u7897 t b\u7853 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u th\u7845 y m\u7845 y con qu\u7927  \u273 \u7849 y m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang \u273 i b\u7897  tr\'ean c\u7847 u xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\u7913 u k\u7883 p, m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i xung quanh d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t m\'e0n kia. \u272 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n khi c\u7853 u ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7885  r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng, nh\'ecn xu\u7889 ng c\u7847 u, ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y x\'e1c ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t \u273 u\u7889 i \u273 ang tr\'f4i n\u7893 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t s\'f4ng. C\'e0ng th\'eam kinh kh\u7911 ng l\'e0 b\u7895 ng nhi\'ean c\'f3 m\u7897 t "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" s\u7855 c m\u7863 t t\'e1i nh\u7907 t, ngo\u7841 i h\'ecnh, \u259 n m\u7863 c gi\u7889 ng h\u7879 t ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a b\u7883  \u273 \u7849 y xu\u7889 ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ch\u7895  c\u7853 u \u273 ang \u273 \u7913 ng, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i th\u7859 ng v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\u432  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 vi\u7879 c g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 "H\uc0\u7855 n" c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 ph\u7843 i v\u7873  nh\'e0, c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n \u273 i tham gia bu\u7893 i t\u7909  h\u7885 p n\'e0o \u273 \'f3, c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7869  gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, v\'f4 th\u7913 c ...h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang s\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i "Ng\u432 \u7901 i" n\'e0o c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  k\u7883 p th\u7901 i t\u7881 nh t\'e1o l\u7841 i nh\u432  T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7847 u tr\u7901 i b\u7883  qu\u7927  kh\'ed x\'e2m nh\u7853 p d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  l\u7841 i t\u7889 i th\'eam.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t th\u7871  gi\u7899 i h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1c qu\uc0\u7927  l\u7897 ng h\'e0nh, \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\'ean \u273 \u7843 o, \u273 \u7883 a ng\u7909 c d\u432 \u417 ng gian, nh\'e2n gian t\u7853 n th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7841 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7841 n b\'e8 b\'ean c\u7841 nh b\u7841 n m\u7895 i ng\'e0y r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i hay ma, c\'f3 khi n\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 \u273 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i b\u7841 n m\'e0 thi th\u7875  c\u7911 a h\u7885  th\u7853 t ra ch\u7881  c\'e1ch b\u7841 n m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c hay kh\'f4ng, m\'e0 t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y. B\u7841 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'fac n\'e0o ma qu\u7927  xung quanh s\u7869  ra tay \u273 o\u7841 t m\u7841 ng m\'ecnh. B\u7841 n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t k\u7867  h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t m\'ecnh s\u7869  l\'e0 ma qu\u7927  \u7849 n n\'fap trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i hay l\'e0 k\u7867  m\'e0 b\u7841 n v\u7851 n coi l\'e0 "Ng\u432 \u7901 i". B\u7841 n th\u7853 m ch\'ed kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t, m\'ecnh r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c c\'f2n s\u7889 ng hay v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t t\u7915  l\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u n\u417 i b\u7841 n v\u7915 a \u273 i qua kia \u273 ang gi\u7845 u thi th\u7875  c\u7911 a b\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, t\u7915 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t ch\u7871 t \u273 i, kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t ai may m\u7855 n tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i, cho \u273 \u7871 n khi th\u7871  gian n\'e0y bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh m\u7897 t "Th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia" .\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7841 n cho r\u7857 ng m\u7885 i s\u7921  v\u7851 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, nh\u432 ng b\'ean ngo\'e0i v\u7867  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7843  th\u7871  gi\u7899 i \u273 \'e3 thay \u273 \u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t th\u7871  gi\u7899 i kinh kh\u7911 ng. M\u7897 t t\u432 \u417 ng lai v\'f4 v\u7885 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ho\'e0n to\'e0n theo b\uc0\u7843 n n\u259 ng \u273 i v\u7873  nh\'e0. C\u7853 u th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7845 y con qu\u7927  \u273 ang r\'ecnh m\'f2 g\u7847 n m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e1m ma qu\u7927  d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang s\u7907  h\'e3i th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng d\'e1m l\u7841 i g\u7847 n c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7901 i d\u7847 n \u273 \u7893  m\u432 a, m\u432 a c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng l\u7899 n, r\u7845 t nhanh c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u432 \u7899 t s\u361 ng, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng g\'ec v\u7899 i m\u7885 i th\u7913  xung quanh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7913 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7917 a nh\'e0, c\u7853 u v\u7915 a t\'ecm th\u7845 y ch\'eca kh\'f3a c\u7917 a \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7903  ra, kh\'ed t\u7913 c \u7845 m \'e1p l\u7853 p t\u7913 c bao quanh c\u7853 u, cu\u7889 n \u273 i h\u417 i n\u432 \u7899 c \u432 \u7899 t l\u7841 nh, c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7917 i th\u7845 y m\'f9i canh c\'e1 r\u7845 t th\u417 m.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi m\u7903  c\u7917 a kh\'f4ng vui nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, nhanh ch\'f3ng k\'e9o c\u7853 u v\'e0o ph\'f2ng, \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i \'f4m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  t\'e2m to\'e0n th\'e2n c\u7853 u \u432 \u7899 t s\u361 ng: "Sao l\u7841 i ch\u7841 y ra ngo\'e0i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh? C\'f2n \u273 \u7875  b\u7883  \u432 \u7899 t th\u7871  n\'e0y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "A Di\'ean, c\'f3 ph\uc0\u7843 i em mu\u7889 n ta sau n\'e0y m\u7897 t t\u7845 c c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\u7901 i m\u7899 i h\'e0i l\'f2ng hay kh\'f4ng?" Nam nh\'e2n n\'f3i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng, b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  \u273 i l\u7845 y qu\u7847 n \'e1o kh\'f4 v\'e0 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c kh\u259 n t\u7855 m l\u7899 n, k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m c\u7903 i h\u7871 t qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \'e3 \u432 \u7899 t, \u273 \u7849 y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng d\u432 \u7899 i v\'f2i sen m\u7903  n\u432 \u7899 c \u7845 m, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u7893 n r\u7891 i m\u7899 i c\u7847 m kh\u259 n lau kh\'f4 cho c\u7853 u, ki\'ean nh\u7851 n m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o cho c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7851 n lu\'f4n ng\'e2y ng\u7889 c, ho\'e0n to\'e0n \u273 \u7875  m\u7863 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi l\'e0m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n l\'ean m\'e1 tr\'e1i c\u7853 u: "A Di\'ean l\'e0m sao v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean h\uc0\u7841  m\u7855 t, tr\'e1nh \'e1nh m\u7855 t h\u7855 n: "Em v\u7915 a nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tin, \u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng m\u7845 t r\u7891 i, Quy\'ean Quy\'ean v\u7851 n ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t, \'f4m c\u7853 u d\u7883 u d\'e0ng an \u7911 i: "Kh\'f4ng sao, A Di\'ean, em c\'f2n c\'f3 ta. Ta s\u7869  lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean em."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\'e2m tr\u7841 ng n\u7863 ng n\u7873  m\'e0 ngu\u7897 i l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c hi\u7875 u r\'f5 l\u7901 i \'f4ng ngo\u7841 i l\'fac \u7845 y, "Ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n kia c\u7911 a con, xung quanh ch\u7881  to\'e0n qu\u7927  kh\'ed v\'e0 \'e2m kh\'ed". L\'fac n\'e0y c\u7853 u c\'f2n th\u7845 y r\'f5 h\u417 n c\u7843  ngo\u7841 i..\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t bao ph\u7911  trong m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng qu\u7927  kh\'ed \u273 en \u273 \u7863 c, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t t\'e1i nh\u7907 t mang theo t\u7917  kh\'ed n\u7863 ng n\u7873 , qu\u7927  kh\'ed t\u7915  tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n cu\u7891 n cu\u7897 c tr\'e0n ra kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng, t\u7909  \u273 \u7871 n b\u7847 u tr\u7901 i b\'ean tr\'ean, b\u7893  sung, d\u7921 ng l\'ean t\u7847 ng t\u7847 ng qu\u7927  kh\'ed k\'e9o d\'e0i kh\'f4ng d\u7913 t. Xuy\'ean qua l\u7899 p qu\u7927  kh\'ed, khu\'f4n m\u7863 t nam nh\'e2n v\u7851 n tu\u7845 n m\u7929  nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c, ch\u7881  l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra r\u7845 t r\'f5 r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e2y tuy\u7879 t \u273 \u7889 i kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 a tay \'f4m ch\u7863 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u d\u7921 a v\'e0o h\u7855 n, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng g\u7885 i: "Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ai hi\uc0\u7875 u r\'f5 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean g\u7889 i h\u417 n c\u7853 u. Ch\u7881  l\'e0 c\u7853 u v\u7851 n lu\'f4n v\u7901  nh\u432  kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y. Trong k\'fd \u7913 c, thi\u7871 u ni\'ean kia y\'ean l\u7863 ng u\u7889 ng c\'e1c lo\u7841 i thu\u7889 c, l\'fac c\u7853 u ng\'e2y th\u417  h\u7887 i c\'f3 \u273 \u7855 ng hay kh\'f4ng s\u7869  quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i \'f4n h\'f2a c\u432 \u7901 i, "Ch\u7881  c\u7847 n c\'f3 th\u7875  \u7903  c\u7841 nh A Di\'ean, \u273 \u7855 ng h\u417 n c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng s\u7907 ". Nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  khi n\'e0o l\u7901 i an \u7911 i c\u7911 a h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh "Ca ca s\u7869  v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n \u7903  b\'ean em". Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia r\'f5 r\u7857 ng h\u7855 n s\u7907  nh\u7845 t kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u7903  b\'ean m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n s\u7869  lu\'f4n c\'f3 th\u7875 . C\'e1i g\'ec h\u7855 n c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng l\u7915 a m\'ecnh. Th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m m\'ecnh b\u7903 i v\'ec l\u7901 i c\u7911 a H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y m\'e0 n\'f3i ra nghi v\u7845 n, h\u7855 n c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\u432 \u7901 i h\u7887 i l\u7841 i "A Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ca ca \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t?", xong l\u7841 i n\'f3i "Ng\u432 \u7901 i H\u7913 a gia b\u7883  qu\u7927  kh\'ed \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng, l\u7901 i c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n \u273 \u7875  trong l\'f2ng". H\u7855 n r\u7845 t kh\'e9o l\'e9o, khi\u7871 n m\'ecnh v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra ch\'e2n t\u432 \u7899 ng h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n che gi\u7845 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7845 t lu\u7853 n x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c n\'f3i g\'ec, d\'f9 cho c\'f3 \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ph\'eda \u273 \u7889 i ngh\u7883 ch th\u7871  gi\u7899 i, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng s\u7869  ki\'ean \u273 \u7883 nh m\'e0 tin t\u432 \u7903 ng \u7911 ng h\u7897  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, nh\u432 ng k\u7867  v\u7841 ch tr\u7847 n h\u7855 n l\u7841 i ch\'ednh l\'e0 h\u7855 n. Hi\u7875 u r\'f5 m\u7885 i c\'e1ch th\u7913 c, ghi ch\'e9p l\u7841 i trong b\'fat k\'fd r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 a cho c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7913 a Th\u7909 y l\'fac \u7845 y n\'f3i kh\'f4ng sai. V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o kh\'f4ng gi\u7871 t B\'e1 Nh\'e2n, nh\u432 ng B\'e1 Nh\'e2n l\u7841 i v\'ec V\u432 \u417 ng \u272 \u7841 o m\'e0 ch\u7871 t. Nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kia kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t ai l\'e0 do Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t, nh\u432 ng h\'ecnh th\'e0nh t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7843 o l\u7897 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng tr\'e1nh kh\u7887 i li\'ean quan. Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca mu\u7889 n \u7903  l\u7841 i th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y, \u273 i\u7873 u n\'e0y kh\'f4ng sai, nh\u432 ng h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ma qu\u7927  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 g\'e2y \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng qu\'e1 l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng h\'f4n l\'ean b\u7901  m\'f4i l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, hai m\u7855 t nh\'ecn h\u7855 n, \u273 \'e1y m\u7855 t \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 s\u432 \u417 ng m\u7901  m\u7883 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ngh\'eanh Chi," c\uc0\u7853 u nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng g\u7885 i h\u7855 n, t\u432 \u803 a nh\u432  l\'e0m n\u361 ng \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883 , "Ng\'e0y mai em mu\u7889 n \u273 i th\u259 m Quy\'ean Quy\'ean, anh \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\u7901  em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? Em mu\u7889 n \u259 n s\u432 \u7901 n kho anh l\'e0m, th\'eam canh \u259 n v\u7899 i c\u417 m n\u7919 a. T\u7889 t nh\u7845 t l\'e0 th\'eam m\u7897 t m\'f3n m\u7863 n m\u7897 t m\'f3n canh. C\'f2n mu\u7889 n \u259 n c\u7843  b\'e1nh nh\'e2n th\u7883 t d\'ea n\u7919 a."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em \uc0\u273 \'fang l\'e0 l\u7855 m y\'eau c\u7847 u, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y ch\u7881  ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n \u259 n." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i, k\'e9o c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 \u7899 c b\'e0n \u259 n ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, b\u432 ng hai b\'e1t canh c\'e1 n\'f3ng h\u7893 i \u273 i ra, "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c, s\u7869  l\'e0m h\u7871 t cho em."\cb1 \
