\f1\b0 \cf2 R\uc0\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m m\u7899 i v\'e0o n\u259 m nh\u7845 t \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 h\u7885 c m\u7897 t b\u7897  m\'f4n. M\'f4n n\'e0y gi\u7843 ng r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u v\u7873  quan \u273 i\u7875 m v\'e0 \u273 \u7883 nh h\u432 \u7899 ng gi\'e1 tr\u7883  c\u7911 a nhi\u7873 u tr\u432 \u7901 ng ph\'e1i tri\u7871 t h\u7885 c kh\'e1c nhau, c\u7911 a Anland, c\u7911 a Nozick, c\u361 ng n\'f3i v\u7873  Rawls v\'e0 Kant, trong gi\u7901  h\u7885 c m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i nghi\'ean c\u7913 u v\u7873  c\'f4ng b\u7857 ng v\'e0 ch\'ednh ngh\u297 a. \cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'f2n nh\u7899  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ti\u7871 t c\u7843  l\u7899 p th\u7843 o lu\u7853 n m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873 : \u273 \u7863 t ra m\u7897 t gi\u7843  thi\u7871 t c\u7921 c \u273 oan, gi\u7843  s\u7917  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'ean A, n\u7871 u nh\u432  gi\u7871 t A, t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7869  s\u7889 ng t\u7889 t h\u417 n, nh\u432  v\u7853 y A c\'f3 \u273 \'e1ng ch\u7871 t kh\'f4ng? N\u7871 u A l\'e0 v\'f4 d\u7909 ng v\u7899 i th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y, gi\u7871 t h\u7855 n th\'ec nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c c\'f3 th\u7875  s\u7889 ng r\u7845 t t\u7889 t, v\u7853 y A c\'f3 \u273 \'e1ng ch\u7871 t hay kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921  c\'e2u h\u7887 i n\'e0y l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e2u h\u7887 i n\u7893 i ti\u7871 ng kh\'e1c v\u7873  t\'e0u \u273 i\u7879 n: m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c t\'e0u \u273 i\u7879 n b\u7883  m\u7845 t \u273 i\u7873 u khi\u7875 n \u273 ang lao \u273 \u7871 n v\u7899 i t\u7889 c \u273 \u7897  cao, \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7871 n c\u7911 a n\'f3 s\u7869  \u273 \'e2m ch\u7871 t m\u432 \u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i, l\'fac n\'e0y trong tay b\u7841 n \u273 ang c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c tay c\u7847 m, n\u7871 u b\u7841 n v\u7863 n tay c\u7847 m, t\'e0u s\u7869  \u273 \u7893 i h\u432 \u7899 ng nh\u432 ng h\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng s\u7869  c\'f3 ba ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  \u273 \'e2m ch\u7871 t. N\u7871 u kh\'f4ng x\'e9t \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1c y\u7871 u t\u7889  quy t\u7855 c x\'e3 h\u7897 i kh\'e1c, ch\u7881  h\u432 \u7899 ng theo gi\'e1 tr\u7883  m\'e0 n\'f3i, b\u7841 n c\'f3 v\u7863 n tay c\u7847 m kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi c\'f2n tr\uc0\u7867  hi\u7875 u bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u, h\u259 ng h\'e1i b\'e0n lu\u7853 n kh\u7855 p n\u417 i, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c quan \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7911 a b\u7843 n th\'e2n v\'f4 c\'f9ng s\'e2u s\u7855 c; sau n\'e0y khi \u273 \'e3 ch\u7913 ng ki\u7871 n nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n hi\u7875 u ra nhi\u7873 u \u273 i\u7873 u r\u7891 i, ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng d\'e1m d\u7877  d\'e0ng \u273 \u432 a ra suy lu\u7853 n nh\u7853 n \u273 \u7883 nh n\u7919 a. B\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7911 a tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh l\'e0 h\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1ch c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u l\u7855 ng nghe nh\u7919 ng ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ng nay Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  t\u7915 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7843 o lu\u7853 n tr\'ean l\u7899 p \u273 \'f3 \'97\'97 n\u7871 u A s\u7889 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t cho th\u7871  gi\u7899 i th\'ec sao? N\u7871 u A, l\u7841 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7841 n y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng nh\u432  m\'e1u th\u7883 t nh\u432  t\'ednh m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i theo ch\u7911  ngh\u297 a th\u7921 c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a Bentham, nh\u432 ng cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7873  lu\u7853 n cu\u7889 i k\u7923 . Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i nh\'e2n v\u7853 t A v\'f4 t\u7897 i ph\u7843 i hi sinh, h\u7855 n ch\'ednh l\'e0 \'e1c qu\u7927  t\'e0 nh\u7845 t th\u7871  gian kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7889 ng l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i d\uc0\u7889 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 i mua ch\'fat \u273 \u7891  b\u7893  \u273 \u7871 n th\u259 m \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean. Th\u7847 n h\u7891 n T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \'e3 ti\'eau t\'e1n, thi th\u7875  c\u7911 a h\u7855 n nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  b\u7883  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n, tr\u432 \u7899 c khi \u273 i T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \'e3 nh\u7901  c\u7853 u gi\u7845 u \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean, nh\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t vi\u7879 c n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  che gi\u7845 u bao l\'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh \u273 \'f3n c\u7853 u v\'e0o nh\'e0, c\'f4 qu\u7903  tr\'e1ch T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m c\u7843  bu\u7893 i, n\'f3i h\u7855 n l\u7841 i \u273 i c\'f4ng t\'e1c, \u273 i r\u7891 i m\u7899 i b\'e1o cho c\'f4 hay, b\u7843 o l\'e0 t\u7841 m th\u7901 i b\u7883  \u273 i\u7873 u \u273 i ch\u7845 p h\'e0nh nhi\u7879 m v\u7909  b\'ed m\u7853 t, nh\u7919 ng ng\'e0y n\'e0y ph\u7843 i t\u7855 t \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i kh\'f4ng li\'ean l\u7841 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. N\'e9t m\u7863 t c\'f4 \u273 \u7847 y v\u7867  o\'e1n tr\'e1ch v\'e0 b\u7845 t m\'e3n, nh\u432 ng c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n l\'e0 nhung nh\u7899  v\'e0 y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  nhi\'ean c\'f4 v\u7851 n ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n. Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 o\'e1n \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 tin nh\u7855 n T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m g\u7917 i cho \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean sau khi r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i nh\'e0 v\'e0 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7897 i v\'e0ng c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u che gi\u7845 u t\'e2m tr\u7841 ng, qua v\'e0i gi\'e2y m\u7899 i ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn b\u7909 ng \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean, c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i: "Kh\'f4ng n\'f3i \u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng n\u7919 a, t\'f4i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y xem con g\'e1i t\'f4i sao r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean c\u361 ng c\u432 \u7901 i: "V\u7851 n ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t l\'e0 trai hay g\'e1i m\'e0, sao c\u7853 u l\u7841 i bi\u7871 t l\'e0 g\'e1i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t gi\u7899 i t\'ednh \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887 , ch\u7859 ng qua l\'e0 khi c\'f2n s\u7889 ng T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\u7849 m b\u7849 m mu\u7889 n sinh con g\'e1i, t\u7889 t h\u417 n l\'e0 gi\u7889 ng \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean, \u273 \u7915 ng nh\u432  m\'ecnh, xong l\u7841 i n\'f3i sinh con trai c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\u7879 , s\u7869  mang n\'f3 \u273 i \u273 \'e1 b\'f3ng. Cho n\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7901 i m\u7855 t v\u7873  ph\'eda thai nhi, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i l\u7853 p t\u7913 c s\u7917 ng s\u7889 t. Thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p tr\'ean m\u7855 t ch\u432 a h\u7871 t t\'e1c d\u7909 ng, c\u7853 u v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai gi\u7899 i \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng, l\'fac n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y r\'f5 ph\u7847 n b\u7909 ng \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean t\u7909  m\u7897 t lu\u7891 ng kh\'ed \u273 en \u273 ang ra s\u7913 c mu\u7889 n chui v\'e0o trong thai nhi, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u b\u7883  d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed h\u417 i y\u7871 u quanh th\'e2n \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean c\u7843 n l\u7841 i n\'ean kh\'f4ng v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Thai nhi ph\'e1t tri\uc0\u7875 n trong c\u417  th\u7875  m\u7865  c\u226 \u768 n h\u7845 p th\u7909  sinh kh\'ed v\'e0 d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed xung quanh, nh\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 i\'ean \u273 \u7843 o, qu\u7927  kh\'ed l\u7853 t tr\u7901 i, d\u432 \u417 ng kh\'ed v\'e0 sinh kh\'ed c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng nh\u7841 t, thai nhi ch\u432 a ra \u273 \u7901 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7921 a v\'e0o sinh kh\'ed t\u7915  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7865  m\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\u7875 n kh\'f3 kh\u259 n, nh\u432 ng xung quanh v\u7851 n c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u ma t\'e0 \u273 ang r\'ecnh r\u7853 p, r\u7909 c r\u7883 ch mu\u7889 n \u273 o\u7841 t l\u7845 y th\'e2n th\u7875  c\'f2n nh\u7887  ch\u432 a ho\'e0n to\'e0n th\'e0nh h\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u c\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u417  th\u7875  \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  n\u7893 i, \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9 c\u361 ng s\u7869  g\u7863 p nguy hi\u7875 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ho\uc0\u7863 c gi\u7843  s\u7917  chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y c\'f2n ch\u432 a x\u7843 y ra, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean ra ngo\'e0i \u273 i b\u7897  c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  ma qu\u7927  c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u tr\u7889 n trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t. \u272 \u7913 a nh\u7887  c\'f2n ch\u432 a ra \u273 \u7901 i s\u7869  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927  thai. .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 ng C\u7849 m v\'ec kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i hai m\u7865  con m\'e0 ch\u7885 n h\u7891 n phi ph\'e1ch t\'e1n, nh\u432 ng ngay c\u7843  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u7903  th\u7871  gi\u7899 i \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7843 o ngh\u7883 ch n\'e0y ch\u432 a ch\u7855 c hai m\u7865  con c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7843 m b\u7843 o an to\'e0n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7845 y c\u7899  \u273 i v\u7879  sinh, \'e2m th\u7847 m c\u7855 n ng\'f3n tr\u7887  tay tr\'e1i d\'f9ng m\'e1u v\u7869  m\u7845 y t\u7845 m ph\'f9 b\'ecnh an \u273 \u432 a cho \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean, b\u7843 o c\'f4 mang theo b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i. Tr\u432 \u7899 c khi \u273 i d\'f9ng ng\'f3n tay ch\u7843 y m\'e1u kh\u7869  vu\u7889 t qua ph\u7847 n b\u7909 ng \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean ph\'e1 tan lu\u7891 ng kh\'ed \u273 en kia, tho\u7841 t nh\'ecn gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang s\u7901  \u273 \u7913 a b\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u, n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean: "C\u7853 u b\u7843 o tr\u7885 ng, nh\u7899  ch\u259 m s\'f3c b\u7843 n th\'e2n cho t\u7889 t. Ti\u7875 u T\u7889 ng nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  l\u7899 n l\'ean b\'ecnh an, sau n\'e0y c\'f2n l\u7907 i h\u7841 i h\u417 n c\u7843  \u272 \u7841 i T\u7889 ng n\u7919 a, s\u7869  tr\u7903  th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'e0i gi\u7887 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7877 n c\u7853 u v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi r\uc0\u7901 i nh\'e0 T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng v\u7873  nh\'e0 m\'e0 \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\'f4ng vi\'ean g\u7847 n \u273 \'f3, t\'ecm m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c tr\u7889 ng ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, l\u7845 y ra t\u7915  trong ba l\'f4 m\u7897 t quy\u7875 n s\'e1ch \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean \u273 \u7847 u g\u7889 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\'e1ch \uc0\u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t c\u361 , trang gi\u7845 y \u7889  v\'e0ng nh\u432  s\u7855 p n\'e1t, gi\u7919 a nhi\u7873 u trang th\u7853 m ch\'ed \u273 \'e3 m\u7911 n ra, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\u7865 p l\u7841 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Quy\uc0\u7875 n s\'e1ch n\'e0y l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong ba quy\u7875 n n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean mang \u273 i t\u7915  Tr\'ec gia, c\u361 ng l\'e0 quy\u7875 n th\'e2m \u7843 o xa x\u432 a nh\u7845 t, c\'e1c ph\'e1p tr\u7853 n thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p ghi ch\'e9p b\'ean trong ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7885 c kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u n\'ean sau khi xem qua m\u7897 t l\u7847 n v\u7851 n ch\u432 a l\u7845 y ra \u273 \u7885 c l\u7841 i, ch\u7881  khi n\'e0o c\u226 \u768 n m\u7899 i l\u7845 y ra xem t\'ecm linh c\u7843 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng c\u7853 u nh\u7899  r\'f5 trong n\'e0y c\'f3 ghi m\u7897 t thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 a t\'e0 linh sang th\u7871  gi\u7899 i b\'ean kia. C\u7853 u c\u361 ng nh\u7899  mang m\'e1ng, c\'e1i gi\'e1 \u273 \u7855 t nh\u7845 t ph\u7843 i tr\u7843  c\u7911 a thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p l\'e0 m\u7841 ng c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i thi thu\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'fai \uc0\u273 \u7847 u, c\u7849 n th\u7853 n l\u7853 t qua l\u7853 t l\u7841 i t\'ecm nh\u7919 ng ch\u7919  c\'f2n nh\u7899  trong \u273 \u7847 u, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7897 i dung mu\u7889 n t\'ecm.\cb1 \
\cb3 "... D\'f9ng chi x\uc0\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0y, nh\u7853 p \u273 \u7847 u tim kia..." Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'ec th\u7847 m, n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i. C\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 nh\u7899  nh\u7847 m, tr\'ean s\'e1ch ghi khi \u273 \'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i thi thu\u7853 t ph\u7843 i tr\'f4ng coi m\u7855 t tr\u7853 n, kh\'f4ng k\u7883 p ch\u7841 y tho\'e1t n\'ean sau khi ch\u7871 t s\u7869  \u273 i c\'f9ng t\'e0 linh sang th\u7871  gi\u7899 i b\'ean kia. \u272 \'e2y ch\'ednh l\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 u c\u7853 u mu\u7889 n, d\'f9 sao tr\'ean th\u7871  gi\u7899 i n\'e0y, ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u \u273 \u7875  \'fd c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 r\uc0\u7857 ng k\u7923  th\u7853 t h\u7855 n v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7885 c l\u7841 i \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n thi thu\u7853 t v\'e0i l\u7847 n, nh\u7899  k\u297  trong l\'f2ng r\u7891 i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n c\u7845 t s\'e1ch l\u7841 i, chu\u7849 n b\u7883  v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Thi thu\uc0\u7853 t c\'f2n c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 i\u7873 u ki\u7879 n kh\'e1c, \u273 \u7873 u d\u7877  th\u7887 a m\'e3n, ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 i\u7873 u kh\'f3 l\'e0m, c\'e1i g\u7885 i l\'e0 "D\'f9ng chi x\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0y, nh\u7853 p \u273 \u7847 u tim kia", l\'e0 ph\u7843 i d\'f9ng x\u432 \u417 ng khi t\'e0 linh c\'f2n s\u7889 ng \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o tim ng\u432 \u7901 i thi thu\u7853 t, d\'ednh m\'e1u n\u417 i \u273 \u7847 u tim m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Tim c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 \u7903  ngay \u273 \'e2y, nh\u432 ng x\u432 \u417 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'ec kh\'f4ng d\u7877  v\'e0o tay nh\u432  v\u7853 y. C\u7853 u nh\u7899  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7915 ng n\'f3i m\u7897  h\u7855 n n\u7857 m \u7903  c\u7845 m \u273 \u7883 a trong n\'fai \u7849 n c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p gia, do ng\u432 \u7901 i Di\u7879 p gia c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i canh ch\u7915 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7891 i tr\'ean xe bu\'fdt v\u7873  nh\'e0, nh\'ecn y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i tr\'e0n ng\u7853 p b\u7889 n ph\'eda l\u7841 i t\u7921  gi\'e1c tr\'e1nh m\'ecnh r\u7845 t xa, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean n\u7893 i l\'ean m\u7897 t \'fd ngh\u297  trong \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 m\uc0\u7897 t vi\u7879 c cho t\u7899 i gi\u7901  c\u7853 u v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \'ea\u777  \'fd \u273 \u234 \u769 n, nh\u7919 ng ma qu\u7927  c\u7845 p th\u7845 p kia \u273 \u7873 u s\u7907  c\u7853 u, m\u7897 t l\'e0 s\u7907  t\'e0 kh\'ed \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t b\u7849 m sinh \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 trong m\'e1u, hai l\'e0 s\u7907  b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi t\u7863 ng c\u7853 u v\'e0o T\u7871 t n\u259 m c\u7853 u l\'ean \u272 \u7841 i h\u7885 c. L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n, d\u7921 a theo l\u7901 i H\u7913 a Th\u7909 y n\'f3i th\'ec v\u7873  sau Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 l\'ean l\'e0m gia ch\u7911  c\u7911 a Di\u7879 p gia, c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t, c\u361 ng b\u7903 i v\'ec \u273 \'e3 ch\u7871 t n\'ean m\u7899 i ch\u7853 m ch\u7841 p kh\'f4ng d\'e1m tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p g\u7863 p c\u7853 u?\cb1 \
\
\cb3 V\uc0\u7853 y l\'fac \u273 \'f3 Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7889 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7863 ng c\u7853 u v\u7853 t g\'ec? R\u7889 t cu\u7897 c trong b\'ecnh s\u7913  ch\u7913 a th\u7913  g\'ec m\'e0 c\'f3 th\u7875  khi\u7871 n y\'eau ma qu\u7927  qu\'e1i s\u7907  h\'e3i \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y? Ng\u432 \u7901 i sau khi ch\u7871 t, r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c s\u7869  \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i v\u7853 t g\'ec m\'e0 \u273 \'e1ng \u273 \u7875  h\u7855 n c\'e1ch tr\u259 m s\'f4ng ngh\'ecn n\'fai \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t g\u7917 i \u273 \u7871 n cho c\u7853 u, d\u7863 n d\'f2 c\u7853 u mang theo b\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng ng\u7891 i y\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y xu\u7889 ng xe, g\u7885 i taxi \u273 \u7871 n c\u7917 a h\'e0ng th\u7911  c\'f4ng m\u7929  ngh\u7879  g\u7847 n nh\u7845 t. Tr\'ean m\u7841 ng n\'f3i ti\u7879 m n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7863 t l\'e0m gia c\'f4ng c\'e1c lo\u7841 i g\u7889 m s\u7913 , h\'e0ng m\u7929  ngh\u7879  ch\u7845 t li\u7879 u kh\'e1c nhau theo y\'eau c\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 i v\'e0o c\u7917 a h\'e0ng tr\u7921 c ti\u7871 p t\'ecm \'f4ng ch\u7911 , th\'e1o b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u273 eo tr\'ean c\u7893  xu\u7889 ng, h\u7887 i: "\'d4ng ch\u7911 , t\'f4i c\'f3 chi\u7871 c b\'ecnh nh\u7887  n\'e0y, \'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o c\u7855 t n\'f3 ra l\u7845 y \u273 \u7891  b\'ean trong m\'e0 kh\'f4ng t\u7893 n h\u7841 i g\'ec r\u7891 i ph\u7909 c h\u7891 i l\u7841 i nguy\'ean tr\u7841 ng nh\u432  c\u361  kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ecnh s\uc0\u7913  nh\u7887  nguy\'ean kh\u7889 i b\'f3ng lo\'e1ng, kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn ra b\u7845 t k\'ec khe h\u7903  n\'e0o, c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c khi ch\u7871  t\'e1c \u273 \'e3 b\u7887  r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u t\'e2m t\u432 . \'d4ng ch\u7911  c\u7847 m trong tay quan s\'e1t m\u7897 t l\'e1t, n\'f3i c\'f3 th\u7875 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u: "\'d4ng c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng? T\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y ch\u7901 . Vi\u7879 c h\u417 i g\u7845 p, t\u259 ng ti\u7873 n ph\'ed c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao."\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 vi\uc0\u7879 c qu\'e1 ph\u7913 c t\u7841 p, \'f4ng ch\u7911  kh\'f4ng ch\'fat do d\u7921  \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng b\'ean c\u7841 nh s\u7889 t ru\u7897 t ch\u7901 , h\'f4 h\u7845 p d\u7847 n tr\u7903  n\'ean g\u7845 p g\'e1p. N\u7871 u c\u7853 u \u273 o\'e1n kh\'f4ng sai, th\u7913  c\u7853 u c\u7847 n c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 ang \u7903  b\'ean trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u7887  b\u7883  t\'e1ch ra, Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng cho \'f4ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7911 , t\u7921  m\'ecnh l\u7845 y ra t\u7915  b\'ean trong m\u7897 t t\'fai v\u7843 i nh\u7887  m\'e0u v\'e0ng, c\u7847 m t\'fai v\u7843 i trong tay r\u7891 i m\u7899 i \u273 \u7875  \'f4ng ch\u7911  b\u7855 t tay v\'e0o ph\u7909 c h\u7891 i b\'ecnh s\u7913  nh\u432  c\u361 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong t\'fai v\uc0\u7843 i ch\u7913 a th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 d\u7841 ng b\u7897 t ph\u7845 n, b\'ean ngo\'e0i l\u7841 i v\u7869  r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u ph\'f9 ch\'fa ph\u7909  linh.\cb1 \

\f2\i \cb3 (*ph\uc0\u7909  linh: t\u259 ng \u273 \u7897  m\u7841 nh, s\u7913 c linh nghi\u7879 m)
