\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\'f4 h\u7845 p ng\u432 ng l\u7841 i. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f2n l\'e0m nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n so v\u7899 i c\u7853 u ph\u7887 ng \u273 o\'e1n. C\u7853 u cho r\u7857 ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  l\'e0 g\u7917 i tro c\u7889 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh cho c\u7853 u gi\'fap c\u7853 u tr\u7915  t\'e0, nh\u432 ng s\u7921  th\u7853 t hi\u7875 n nhi\'ean kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  nh\u432  v\u7853 y, t\u7915 ng t\u7845 m ph\'f9 kia r\'f5 r\'e0ng cho th\u7845 y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'edt nh\u7845 t \u273 \'e3 bu\u7897 c m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n th\u7847 n h\u7891 n c\u7911 a ch\'ednh m\'ecnh v\'e0o ch\u7895  tro c\u7889 t n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c kia c\u7853 u cho r\u7857 ng nh\u7919 ng l\u7847 n c\u7853 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'f3a gi\u7843 i nguy nan g\u7863 p d\u7919  h\'f3a l\'e0nh l\'e0 do Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi thi ph\'e1p, b\'e2y gi\u7901  nh\'ecn l\u7841 i. r\'f5 r\'e0ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7901 i th\u7901 i kh\u7855 c kh\u7855 c ch\'fa \'fd \u273 \u7871 n c\u7853 u, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m c\u7853 u g\u7863 p nguy hi\u7875 m s\u7869  t\u7921  m\'ecnh ra tay t\u7899 i c\u7913 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng t\uc0\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 ngh\u297  t\u7899 i \u273 \'eam \u7903  mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na kia. T\'ecnh h\'ecnh khi \u273 \'f3 nguy hi\u7875 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, t\'ednh m\u7841 ng ng\'e0n c\'e2n treo s\u7907 i t\'f3c, Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca t\u7841 i sao m\u7897 t m\u7921 c kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u ra tay? Sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ng\u7849 n ng\u432 \u7901 i. C\u7853 u ngh\u297  t\u7899 i m\u7897 t kh\u7843  n\u259 ng, m\u7897 t kh\u7843  n\u259 ng m\'e0 b\u7845 t k\u7875  c\u7853 u ngh\u297  th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng \u273 \u7873 u h\u7907 p l\'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u7883  th\u7913  g\'ec ng\u259 n c\u7843 n kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ra tay m\'e0 l\'e0 khi h\u7855 n xu\u7845 t th\u7911 , ch\'ednh m\'ecnh l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'e0o c\'f3 chuy\uc0\u7879 n tr\'f9ng h\u7907 p nh\u432  v\u7853 y, th\u7913  kia r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\'f3 th\u7875  thay ng\'e0y \u273 \u7893 i \u273 \'eam, s\u7889 ng trong mi\u7871 u th\u7847 n Na \u273 \'e3 l\'e2u l\u7841 i khoanh tay \u273 \u7913 ng nh\'ecn, nh\u432 ng ch\u7901  t\u7899 i khi c\u7853 u \u273 \u7871 n l\u7841 i quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh ra tay ph\'e1 v\u7905  m\'ea ch\u432 \u7899 ng \u7903  th\'f4n H\'e0 Gia? C\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7847 n linh n\'e0o s\u7869  r\u7843 nh r\u7895 i \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y, c\u7913 u m\u7841 ng c\u7853 u ch\u7881  v\'ec \u273 \'f2i m\u7897 t n\u7909  h\'f4n. Ch\u432 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p kia t\'e1c d\u7909 ng gi\u7889 ng h\u7879 t trong b\'fat k\'fd c\'f9ng v\u7899 i n\u259 ng l\u7921 c d\u7877  d\'e0ng h\'fat \u273 i qu\u7927  kh\'ed tr\'ean kh\'f4ng trong th\'f4n. Qu\u7927  kh\'ed \u7903  \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i h\u7855 n m\'e0 n\'f3i kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng nh\u7855 c \u273 \u7871 n, \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n b\u7903 i tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n c\'f2n c\'f3 qu\u7927  kh\'ed c\'f2n d\'e0y \u273 \u7863 c h\u417 n ng\'e0n l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  gian n\'e0y sao l\u7841 i c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i x\u7845 u xa nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Bi\u7871 t r\'f5 h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i th\u7913  g\'ec t\u7889 t, r\'f5 r\'e0ng c\u361 ng t\u7913 c gi\u7853 n, nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 c\'e0ng th\'eam y\'eau h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi...\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong l\'fac c\uc0\u7853 u xu\u7845 t th\u7847 n \'f4ng ch\u7911  \u273 \'e3 ph\u7909 c h\u7891 i xong b\'ecnh s\u7913 . Nh\'ecn k\u7929  v\u7851 n c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra m\u7897 t \'edt khuy\u234 \u769 t \u273 i\'ea\u777 m nho\u777  v\'e0 khe h\u7903 , nh\u432 ng li\u7871 c s\u417  qua th\'ec th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'e1c tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7843 m \u417 n \'f4ng ch\u7911 , \u273 eo b\'ecnh s\u7913  l\u7841 i l\'ean c\u7893 , \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i m\u7903  t\'fai v\u7843 i nh\u7887  trong tay, n\'f3i: "C\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t vi\u7879 c mu\u7889 n l\'e0m phi\u7873 n \'f4ng. Nh\u7901  \'f4ng l\'e0m gi\'fap t\'f4i m\u7897 t thanh dao g\u259 m, tr\u7897 n b\u7897 t ph\u7845 n n\'e0y v\'e0o, t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y xem \'f4ng l\'e0m." C\u7853 u nh\'ecn h\'e0ng m\u7851 u trong ti\u7879 m, m\u7897 t v\'e0i lo\u7841 i \u273 ao ki\u7871 m treo trong nh\'e0 \u273 \u7875  trang tr\'ed c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u7863 t l\'e0m theo y\'eau c\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u432 a \'f4ng ch\u7911  th\'eam \'edt ti\u7873 n: "Ti\u7879 n th\u7875  \'f4ng m\'e0i dao gi\'fap t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 ? G\u7847 n \u273 \'e2y m\u7885 i vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng nh\u432  \'fd, \u273 \u7841 i s\u432  b\u7843 o t\'f4i treo m\u7897 t con dao tr\u7915  t\'e0 trong ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch, n\'f3i l\'e0 ph\u7843 i m\'e0i dao s\u7855 c m\u7899 i c\'f3 t\'e1c d\u7909 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 v\'ec tr\u7915  t\'e0. Ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7853 u y\'eau nh\u7845 t kia, v\u7889 n \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 t\'e0.\cb1 \
