\f1\b0 \cf2 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u7847 m dao \u273 \'e3 m\'e0i s\u7855 c c\u7845 t v\'e0o ba l\'f4 r\u7891 i tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\'e0. C\u7853 u th\u7917  dao, \u273 \u7897  s\u7855 c kh\'e1 \u7893 n, \'edt nh\u7845 t \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c y\'eau c\u7847 u c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ec l\'e0m con dao n\'e0y m\'e0 \'f4ng ch\uc0\u7911  ti\u7879 m k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t nh\'e0 x\u432 \u7903 ng th\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7907 p t\'e1c \u7903  v\'f9ng ngo\u7841 i th\'e0nh, \u273 \u7907 i \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac l\'e0m xong m\u7885 i th\u7913  quay tr\u7903  v\u7873  th\'ec \u273 \'e3 h\u417 n b\u7843 y gi\u7901  t\u7889 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7855 t xe v\u7873  nh\'e0, v\u7915 a v\'e0o t\u7899 i c\u7917 a \u273 \'e3 nghe m\'f9i canh s\u432 \u7901 n ninh th\u417 m n\u7913 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o ph\'f2ng thay qu\uc0\u7847 n \'e1o r\u7891 i \u273 i ra, tr\'ean b\'e0n c\u417 m b\'e0y hai \u273 \u297 a th\u7913 c \u259 n, m\u7897 t \u273 \u297 a t\u7887 i x\'e0o m\u7897 t \u273 \u297 a rau x\'e0o, \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\'f3n Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'edch. \u7902  gi\u7919 a \u273 \u7863 t m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c n\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 t m\'e0u v\'e0ng nh\u7841 t \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7853 y n\u7855 p nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng ng\u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'f9i th\u417 m h\u7845 p d\u7851 n t\u7915  trong bay ra. Ngo\'e0i ra c\'f2n c\'f3 m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c n\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 t l\u7899 n kh\'e1c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7903  n\u7855 p ra xem, b\'ean trong l\'e0 ng\'e2n nh\u297 , c\u7849 u k\u7927 , c\'f2n c\'f3 l\'ea c\u7855 t qu\'e2n c\u7901 , l\'e0 canh h\'f4m qua c\u7853 u \u273 \'f2i \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'f4n ba b\'ean ngo\'e0i m\uc0\u7897 t ng\'e0y, b\u7909 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m k\'eau vang, hai m\u7855 t nh\'ecn n\u7891 i s\u432 \u7901 n \u273 \u7873 u tr\u7907 n l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi b\u432 ng m\u7897 t \u273 \u297 a s\u7913  \u273 i ra t\u7915  ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p, \u273 \u7863 t \u273 \u297 a xu\u7889 ng b\'e0n, nh\'ecn c\u7853 u cong kh\'f3e mi\u7879 ng: "Sao v\u7873  mu\u7897 n v\u7853 y, c\'f2n th\'e8m th\'e0nh th\u7871  kia?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u297 a l\'e0 b\'e1nh nh\'e2n th\u7883 t d\'ea \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\'e1n v\'e0ng r\u7897 m, Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\u7901 i m\u7855 t kh\u7887 i \u273 \u297 a, n\'f3i ra l\'ed do \u273 \'e3 s\u7899 m chu\u7849 n b\u7883  : "T\u7889 ng C\u7849 m kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u7903  \u273 \'e2y n\'ean em c\'f9ng Quy\'ean Quy\'ean \u273 i b\u7879 nh vi\u7879 n ki\u7875 m tra, c\u7843  ng\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  trong vi\u7879 n, ch\u432 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u259 n g\'ec c\u7843 ." Ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  c\'e2u cu\u7889 i, nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i kh\'e1c \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 c\u7853 u b\u7883 a ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\u7845 y c\u7853 u th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 \'f3i s\u7855 p h\u7871 t ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i li\u7873 n l\u7845 y b\'e1t \u273 \u361 a cho c\u7853 u \u259 n, tr\'ean b\'e0n c\u417 m l\u7841 i h\u7887 i th\u259 m \u272 \'e0o Quy\'ean Quy\'ean v\'e0 \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 "M\uc0\u7885 i th\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u \u7893 n, ch\u7881  l\'e0 c\u417  th\u7875  h\u417 i k\'e9m." Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 "V\uc0\u7853 y \'e0," Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi g\u7855 p m\u7897 t mi\u7871 ng s\u432 \u7901 n cho Tr\'ec Di\'ean, thu\u7853 n mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i, "H\'f4m n\'e0o ta v\u7899 i em c\'f9ng \u273 i th\u259 m."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \'e1p m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, m\u432 \u7907 n vi\u7879 c g\u7863 m s\u432 \u7901 n m\'e0 c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1nh m\u7855 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 i h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t d\'ednh Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\u417 m n\u432 \u7899 c thu d\u7885 n xong Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ng\u7891 i \u7903  sofa ph\'f2ng kh\'e1ch \u273 \u7885 c s\'e1ch, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng nhanh ch\'f3ng b\'e1m theo, ng\u7891 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng chui v\'e0o trong ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n, th\u7915 a l\'fac h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd v\u7909 ng tr\u7897 m h\'f4n ng\u432 \u7901 i ta.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u7847 m s\'e1ch ng\u7891 i, m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  gi\u7843  v\u7901  b\'ecnh th\u7843 n, nh\u432 ng l\'fac sau y\u7871 t h\u7847 u b\u7883  Tr\'ec Di\'ean ng\u7853 m trong mi\u7879 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng m\'fat c\u7855 n, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7847 u h\u7841  nh\u432  v\u7853 y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i, \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i bu\'f4ng s\'e1ch ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u d\u7921 a v\'e0o sofa, dung t\'fang l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o m\'e0 vu\u7889 t ve t\'f3c Tr\'ec Di\'ean, th\u7903  d\'e0i n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean, sao h\'f4m nay l\u7841 i n\u7883 nh ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7871  n\'e0y? C\'f3 ph\u7843 i l\'e9n l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n x\u7845 u g\'ec sau l\u432 ng ca ca kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bu\'f4ng y\uc0\u7871 t h\u7847 u h\u7855 n, qu\u7923  g\u7889 i ng\u7891 i b\'ean ph\u7843 i m\'e9p sofa, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u qu\u7845 n qu\'edt h\'f4n m\'f4i h\'f4n c\u7857 m h\u7855 n, h\'e0m h\u7891  n\'f3i: "M\u7899 i kh\'f4ng l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n x\u7845 u, ch\u7881  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n anh c\'f9ng em \u273 i ng\u7855 m sao."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7899 n \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 th\'edch thi\'ean v\u259 n, l\u7841 i l\'e0 Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\'ecn c\u7853 u tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh, Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'f3 tin qu\u7927  c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng tin c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'fd do g\'ec l\u7841 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean mu\u7889 n \u273 i ng\u7855 m sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u417 i tr\'e1nh sang b\'ean tr\'e1i, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, s\u7855 c m\u7863 t tho\'e1ng nghi\'eam ngh\u7883 : "N\'f3i th\u7853 t."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng m\'e0 \uc0\u273 u\u7893 i theo, \'f4m ch\u7863 t h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng tay, g\u7885 i t\'ean h\u7855 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi... \u273 i c\'f9ng em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  sau khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m tu\u7893 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\u7845 y c\u7853 u l\'e0m n\u361 ng nh\u432  v\u7853 y. H\u7855 n th\u7853 t s\u7921  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng ch\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, b\u7845 t \u273 \u7855 c d\u297  m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7895  v\u7895  l\u432 ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, tr\u432 \u7899 c ti\'ean \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean \u273 \'e3, ta \u273 i v\u7899 i em." \u272 \u7915 ng n\'f3i ng\u7855 m sao, h\'e1i sao h\u7855 n c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng t\u7915  ch\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean bi\uc0\u7871 t l\'e1i xe, c\u361 ng c\'f3 b\u7857 ng l\'e1i nh\u432 ng v\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f3 xe n\'ean b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e1i. T\'e0i x\u7871  Di\u7879 p gia ch\u7841 y xe \u273 \u7871 n d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7847 u \u273 \'f3n hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, h\u7855 n ph\u7843 i mang xe \u273 \u7871 n cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi li\u7871 c m\u7855 t, t\'e0i x\u7871  tuy kh\'f4ng tin n\u259 ng l\u7921 c c\u7911 a v\u7883  ti\u7875 u thi\u7871 u gia n\'e0y nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nghe l\u7879 nh giao ch\'eca kh\'f3a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u361 ng may nh\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'e1ch n\'fai T\'e2y n\u417 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  mu\u7889 n \u273 i t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i g\u7847 n, th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, bu\u7893 i chi\u7873 u kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 s\u7847 m u\u7845 t, xe c\u7897  c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'f4ng, kh\u7843  n\u259 ng l\'e1i xe c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7889 t h\u417 n Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ngh\u297  nhi\u7873 u, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n n\'fai T\'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7905  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7853 m r\'e3i \u273 i l\'ean, d\'f9 r\u7857 ng hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca ho\'e0n to\'e0n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7889 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 b\u7879 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i \u7903  m\u7897 t kho\u7843 ng \u273 \u7845 t b\u7857 ng gi\u7919 a s\u432 \u7901 n n\'fai. D\'f9 \u273 \'e3 v\'e0o h\u7841  nh\u432 ng ban \u273 \'eam trong n\'fai v\u7851 n h\u417 i l\u7841 nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\u432 ng \u273 eo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c balo l\u7899 n c\'f2n x\'e1ch theo m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c t\'fai kh\'e1c, b\'ean trong chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7911  c\'e1c th\u7913 , c\u7853 u l\u7845 y ra t\u7915  trong t\'fai m\u7897 t t\u7845 m v\u7843 i nh\u7921 a tr\u7843 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t, b\u7887  hai chi\u7871 c \u273 \u7879 m l\'ean, l\u7841 i l\u7845 y ra m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c ch\u259 n m\u7887 ng l\u7899 n, \u273 \u7907 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i d\'f9ng ch\u259 n qu\u7845 n c\u7843  hai l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i: "Chu\u7849 n b\u7883  r\u7845 t \u273 \u7847 y \u273 \u7911 ."\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n nh\'ecn balo c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "Trong balo \u273 \u7921 ng g\'ec v\u7853 y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'e9o balo l\uc0\u7845 y ra hai chai r\u432 \u7907 u, c\'f2n c\'f3 b\'f2 kh\'f4, c\'e1c lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7891  \u259 n v\u7863 t, \u273 \u432 a m\u7897 t chai cho Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "U\u7889 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'e2m tr\u7847 m nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, nh\u7853 n l\u7845 y nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7903  ra, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng n\'f3i: "A Di\'ean, em \u273 \'e3 b\u7843 o ta ph\u7843 i nghe l\u7901 i b\'e1c s\u297 , kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e9p u\u7889 ng r\u432 \u7907 u."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ch\uc0\u7881  hai ch\'fang ta m\u7899 i u\u7889 ng th\'f4i." Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i g\u7847 n h\'f4n h\u7855 n, "Ca ca u\u7889 ng c\'f9ng em m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi kh\'f4ng n\'f3i ti\u7871 p, m\u7903  n\u7855 p chai. M\u7841 ng n\'e0y c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  cho c\u7853 u, hu\u7889 ng chi l\'e0 u\u7889 ng r\u432 \u7907 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean u\uc0\u7889 ng r\u432 \u7907 u, k\u7875  l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n b\u7843 n th\'e2n sau khi r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia, th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng l\u7841 i c\u7909 ng chai v\u7899 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi. Chuy\u7879 n c\u7853 u quay v\u7873  Tr\'ec gia l\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 v\'e0 g\u7863 p l\u7841 i Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng n\'f3i ra, ch\u7881  c\'f3 \u273 i\u7873 u c\u7853 u kh\'f4ng k\u7875  trong qu\'e3ng th\u7901 i gian \u273 \'f3, c\u7853 u nh\u7899  h\u7855 n nhi\u7873 u th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i t\uc0\u7899 i n\'f3i lui, Tr\'ec Di\'ean quay \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca, nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, v\'ec sao kh\'f4ng \u273 i t\'ecm em? V\'ec sao anh cam l\'f2ng \u273 \u7875  em m\u7897 t m\'ecnh?" N\'f3i xong m\u7855 t c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 h\u417 i \u273 \u7887  l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nh\u432  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y thi\u7871 u ni\'ean m\u432 \u7901 i s\'e1u tu\u7893 i n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 c\'f4 \u273 \u7897 c b\u7845 t l\u7921 c r\u7901 i kh\u7887 i Tr\'ec gia, thi\u7871 u ni\'ean h\u7855 n \'f4m trong l\'f2ng c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u b\u7843 y n\u259 m l\u7841 i b\u7883  b\u7913 c b\'e1ch \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\u7855 t \u273 \u7913 t m\u7885 i li\'ean h\u7879  v\u7899 i h\u7855 n. \u272 \'e3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m tr\'f4i qua, l\'fac n\'e0y l\u7841 i truy v\u7845 n h\u7855 n khi \u7845 y v\'ec sao kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd t\u7899 i m\'ecnh, v\'ec sao kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7893  h\u7885 ng nh\u432  b\u7883  ngh\u7865 n, n\'f3i kh\'f4ng n\'ean l\u7901 i. H\u7855 n c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t h\'f4n l\'ean m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, m\u7897 t l\'e1t sau m\u7899 i n\'f3i: "Khi \u273 \'f3 s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e ca ca kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t, v\u7873  sau l\u7841 i l\'ean l\'e0m gia ch\u7911  Di\u7879 p gia, qu\u7843  th\u7921 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tinh l\u7921 c, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian tr\u7889 ng. L\'e0 ca ca kh\'f4ng t\u7889 t." Ch\'ednh h\u7855 n c\u361 ng th\u7845 y l\u7901 i gi\u7843 i th\'edch n\'e0y kh\'f4ng xu\'f4i tai th\u7871  n\'e0o, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n lu\'f4n n\u7857 m th\u7913  nh\u7845 t trong l\'f2ng h\u7855 n, n\u7871 u nh\u432  c\'f3 th\u7875 , n\u7871 u nh\u432  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ph\'e9p, h\u7855 n sao l\u7841 i cam l\'f2ng kh\'f4ng \u273 i g\u7863 p c\u7853 u .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i n\u7919 a, ch\u7881  "V\'e2ng" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng nh\u432  ch\u7845 p nh\u7853 n l\u7901 i gi\u7843 i th\'edch, h\u7887 i m\u7897 t v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  kh\'e1c: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 Di\u7879 p gia r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c x\u7843 y ra chuy\u7879 n g\'ec? V\'ec sao b\'e1c v\'e0 hai anh \u273 \u7873 u l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t \u273 i, ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh anh?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\u7841  m\u7855 t: "Cha ta \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n tu\u7893 i, qua \u273 \u7901 i b\'ecnh an, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \'f4ng \u7845 y ngh\u297  th\u7871  n\'e0o, di ng\'f4n n\'f3i mu\u7889 n giao v\u7883  tr\'ed gia ch\u7911  cho ta. Hai anh trai c\u7911 a ta tranh gi\'e0nh nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 \u7907 i nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng cam t\'e2m, cho n\'ean cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  li\'ean th\u7911  mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ch\u7871 t ta. K\u7871 t qu\u7843  kh\'f4ng\'a0 ng\u7901  ng\u432 \u7907 c l\u7841 i b\u7883  ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  ch\u7871 t. Chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y n\'f3i ra kh\'f4ng d\u7877  nghe, ta n\'f3i v\u7899 i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7857 ng h\u7885  b\u7883  nhi\u7877 m b\u7879 nh c\u7845 p t\'ednh m\'e0 ch\u7871 t." Tr\'ec Di\'ean mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i, nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean h\u7855 n s\u7869  kh\'f4ng gi\u7845 u.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ngh\uc0\u297  t\u7899 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi nghe xong l\u7841 i h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p: "B\u7885 n h\u7885  ch\u7871 t nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7883  ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  ch\u7871 t." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\u361 ng ki\'ean nh\u7851 n l\u7863 p l\u7841 i m\u7897 t l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\'ecn h\uc0\u7855 n: "B\u7883  ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o?"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi thay \u273 \u7893 i s\u7855 c m\u7863 t, ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "A Di\'ean, em nghe ai n\'f3i g\'ec \u432 ? C\'e1i ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0 gieo gi\'f3 g\u7863 t b\'e3o."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em bi\uc0\u7871 t." Tr\'ec Di\'ean \'f4m h\u7855 n, d\u7921 a v\'e0o tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7921 c h\u7855 n, "Em ch\u7881  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n bi\u7871 t r\'f5, b\u7885 n h\u7885  b\u7883  ph\u7843 n ph\u7879  nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o."\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i, c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n \u273 \u7881 nh \u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u b\u7847 u tr\u7901 i \u273 \'eam, kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 u: "A Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\uc0\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  nghe Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi tr\u7847 m gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ta b\u7879 nh th\'e0nh c\'e1i d\u7841 ng kia, b\u7843 n th\'e2n kh\'f4ng s\u7889 ng n\u7893 i m\u7845 y ng\'e0y, mu\u7889 n r\u7901 i Di\u7879 p gia \u273 i g\u7863 p em m\u7897 t l\u7847 n cu\u7889 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. B\u7885 n h\u7885  nh\u7845 t quy\u7871 t kh\'f4ng ch\u7901 , sau khi mua chu\u7897 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u7911 a ta \u273 \'e3 b\'e0y t\u7909  t\'e0 tr\u7853 n mu\u7889 n h\u7841 i ta, sau khi ta t\u7855 t th\u7903  l\u7853 p t\u7913 c h\'f3a qu\u7927 , qu\u7927  kh\'ed ngh\u7883 ch d\'f2ng, to\'e0n b\u7897  ng\u432 \u7901 i thi thu\u7853 t b\u7883  ph\u7843 n ph\u7879 , kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t ai s\u7889 ng." Thanh \'e2m xa x\u259 m, d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  \u273 ang k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan t\u7899 i m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \'f4m Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean \u273 \'f9i, th\'e2n m\u7853 t c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n ch\'f3p m\u361 i c\u7853 u, n\'f3i kh\u7869 : "Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i em mu\u7889 n nghe ca ca n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng? Mu\u7889 n ca ca n\'f3i cho em nghe r\u7857 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t? N\'f3i cho em bi\u7871 t r\u7857 ng, ta kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\'e1ch n\'e0o \u273 i g\u7863 p em, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7903 i v\'ec khi \u273 \'f3 b\u7883  b\u7879 nh \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i ngay c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng m\'e0 b\u7903 i v\'ec ta \u273 \'e3 tri\u7879 t \u273 \u7875  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh qu\u7927 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 "Ta c\uc0\u361 ng bi\u7871 t, n\'fai \u7849 n bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y ph\u7847 n l\u7899 n v\'ec ta sau khi ch\u7871 t ng\'e0y ng\'e0y \u273 \'eam \u273 \'eam kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng sinh ra qu\u7927  kh\'ed. Nh\u432 ng l\u7841 i ta kh\'f4ng b\u7887  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c em, m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u l\'e0 kh\'f4ng cam l\'f2ng n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7863 p em, v\u7873  sau l\u7841 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y, n\u7871 u ta d\u7913 t kho\'e1t \u273 i, \u273 \u7875  l\u7841 i em cho ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c, nh\u432  th\u7871  so v\u7899 i ch\u7871 t \u273 i ta l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i. A Di\'ean, ta mu\u7889 n c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i \u7903  b\'ean em, c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895  v\u7899 i em, cho d\'f9 gi\u7843  v\u7901  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i g\u7841 t em c\u7843  \u273 \u7901 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng sao. B\'e2y gi\u7901  em \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u259 m gh\'e9t ta, h\u7853 n ta, s\u7907  ta hay kh\'f4ng? C\u7843 m th\u7845 y gi\'e1 m\'e0 l\'fac \u7845 y ta c\u7913  th\u7871  ch\u7871 t \u273 i, c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n, s\u7869  kh\'f4ng x\u7843 y ra nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ra s\uc0\u7913 c l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u. C\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5 r\u7889 t cu\u7897 c m\'ecnh mu\u7889 n ph\u7911  nh\u7853 n \u273 i\u7873 u g\'ec, ch\u7881  m\u7897 t m\u7921 c l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u, sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7893  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, s\'e1t l\u7841 i g\u7847 n h\'f4n h\u7855 n c\u7855 n x\'e9 m\'f4i h\u7855 n, kh\'f4ng cho h\u7855 n n\'f3i ti\u7871 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'ecnh c\uc0\u7853 u g\u7863 m c\u7855 n d\u7847 n d\u7847 n bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh m\u7897 t n\u7909  h\'f4n s\'e2u th\u7853 t d\'e0i, sau khi t\'e1ch ra Tr\'ec Di\'ean t\u7921 a \u273 \u7847 u d\u432 \u7899 i c\u7857 m Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi, ngh\u7865 n ng\'e0o g\u7885 i t\'ean h\u7855 n: "Ngh\'eanh Chi..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Em y\'eau anh, b\uc0\u7845 t lu\u7853 n anh tr\u7903  th\'e0nh th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 i n\u7919 a, em \u273 \u7873 u y\'eau anh, v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  l\'e0 t\'ecnh y\'eau n\'e0y ch\'f4n gi\u7845 u qu\'e1 s\'e2u, th\u7853 t kh\'f3 c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i ra tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng c\u7853 u ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean, \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'ea mang ph\u7911  m\u7897 t t\u7847 ng h\u417 i n\u432 \u7899 c nh\'ecn Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi: "Ngh\'eanh Chi, n\u7871 u em \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t th\u7871  gi\u7899 i kh\'e1c, anh c\'f3 b\u7857 ng l\'f2ng \u273 i c\'f9ng em kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ean ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\u7855 n t\'e0 kh\'ed qu\u7927  kh\'ed qu\'e1 th\u7883 nh, h\u417 n n\u7919 a s\u7869  c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng m\'e3nh li\u7879 t, n\u7871 u c\u7913  ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c, kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 n\'fai \u7849 n, kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  th\'e0nh ph\u7889  R, c\u7843  th\u7871  gian n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u s\u7869  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y. B\u7885 n h\u7885  tr\u7889 n \u7903  \u273 \'e2u c\u361 ng v\'f4 d\u7909 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 "B\uc0\u7857 ng l\'f2ng" Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn c\u7853 u, ng\'f3n c\'e1i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng vu\u7889 t ve m\u7855 t c\u7853 u, "B\u7845 t lu\u7853 n em \u273 i \u273 \'e2u, ta s\u7869  lu\'f4n \u7903  b\'ean em."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n k\'e9o Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0o ng\u7921 c: "A Di\'ean c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng v\u297 nh vi\u7877 n \u7903  b\'ean ta."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\uc0\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u bi\u7871 t, Ngh\'eanh Chi ca ca nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  b\u7857 ng l\'f2ng \u7903  c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7901 i \u273 \'eam t\u7889 i \u273 en \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'f3 k\'e9o m\u7897 t v\u7879 t s\'e1ng k\'e9o d\'e0i, m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 m\u7897 t v\'e0i v\u7879 t \u273 \u417 n l\u7867 , r\u7845 t nhanh \u273 \'e3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh nhi\u7873 u v\u7879 t l\u7899 n. L\'e0 m\u432 a sao b\u259 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn tr\u7901 i \u273 \'eam: "Tr\'e1ch kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean \u273 \'f2i \u273 i ng\u7855 m sao... A Di\'ean!"\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i c\'f2n ch\u432 a d\u7913 t, gi\u7885 ng h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  n\'ean run r\u7849 y m\'e0 tuy\u7879 t v\u7885 ng, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y t\u7853 n th\u7871 . Tuy r\u7857 ng t\u7853 n th\u7871  th\u7853 t s\u7921  \u273 ang b\'e0y tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t h\u7855 n, h\u7855 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n th\u7901  \u417 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7845 y ra t\u7915  trong ba l\'f4 m\u7897 t con dao g\u259 m, th\u7915 a d\u7883 p m\u7897 t kh\u7855 c Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u kia l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \'e2m v\'e0o tim m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Theo \uc0\u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c c\u7911 a c\u7853 u, t\u7845 m v\u7843 i nh\u7921 a tr\u7843 i tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t ph\u7843 n chi\u7871 u \'e1nh sao s\'e1ng r\u7905  tr\'ean tr\u7901 i ph\'e1t ra tia s\'e1ng y\u7871 u \u7899 t, \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 ph\'e1p tr\u7853 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\'f9ng m\'e1u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\u7869  ra t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c. S\u7855 c \u273 \'eam t\u7889 i m\u7901  l\u7841 i c\'f3 \u273 \u7879 m che khi\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f3 m\'e0 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Di\uc0\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\u7853 u, m\u7897 t c\'e2u l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i n\'ean l\u7901 i, cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ch\u7881  nghi\u7871 n r\u259 ng ra ba ch\u7919 : "... Ti\u7875 u b\u7841 i ho\u7841 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean n\'edu l\uc0\u7845 y \'e1o h\u7855 n, \'e1nh m\u7855 t quy\u7871 n luy\u7871 n kh\'f4ng th\'f4i: "Ca ca \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i s\u7869  lu\'f4n b\'ean em. Anh c\'f3 o\'e1n..." C\u7853 u mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i anh c\'f3 o\'e1n em kh\'f4ng, nh\u432 ng v\'e0i ch\u7919  cu\u7889 i \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7913 c n\'f3i ra mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'e9t m\uc0\u7863 t Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4i ph\u7909 c b\'ecnh t\u297 nh, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \'f4m c\u7853 u: "Kh\'f4ng o\'e1n, \'edt nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m ta c\'f2n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\u417  th\u7875  c\'f2n mang theo nhi\u7879 t \u273 \u7897  \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng \'f4m em. Ta kh\'f4ng o\'e1n."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i h\u7855 n n\'f3i ch\'ednh l\'e0, \u7903  ki\u7871 p n\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng \'f4m ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng c\'f2n g\'ec o\'e1n h\u7853 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7845 m sao tr\'ean tr\u7901 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n h\u7897 i t\u7909  v\'e2y quanh b\u7885 n h\u7885 , Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi h\'f4n Tr\'ec Di\'ean, nh\'ecn ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau trong l\'f2ng m\'ecnh nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean li\u7871 c m\u7897 t c\'e1i c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn th\u7845 u t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a thu\u7853 t ph\'e1p n\'e0y. A Di\'ean th\'e0 r\u7857 ng ch\u7871 t c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n k\'e9o h\u7855 n \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t th\u7871  gi\u7899 i kh\'e1c, v\u7853 y h\u7855 n s\u7869  c\'f9ng \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7855 n ch\u7881  \u273 au l\'f2ng, m\u7897 t dao kia, qu\'e1 \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n.\cb1 \
