\cf2 \cb3 Edit by An Nhi\'ean\cb1 \
\cb3 Xa xa t\uc0\u7889 i \u273 en kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 i\u7875 m cu\u7889 i, ch\u7881  c\'f3 ch\'fat \'e1nh s\'e1ng l\u7901  m\u7901  xung quanh. Nh\u432 ng ch\'fat s\'e1ng n\'e0y l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  gi\u7843 m b\u7899 t c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907  v\'e0 b\'ed b\u7913 c c\u7911 a khung c\u7843 nh n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y m\'e0 c\'f2n ph\'f3ng \u273 \u7841 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c qu\u7927  d\u7883  l\'fac n\'e0y\'97\'97 \u7903  nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i \'e1nh s\'e1ng chi\u7871 u t\u7899 i tr\'ean v\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng hai b\'ean tr\'e1i ph\u7843 i xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n v\'f4 s\u7889  h\'ecnh b\'f3ng v\u7863 n v\u7865 o m\'e0u \u273 en, ngay ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng nh\'ecn ra h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i, ph\'eda sau th\'ec ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra b\'f3ng \u273 en kh\'f4ng r\'f5. Ch\'fang chen l\u7845 n d\u7891 n l\'ean, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n ti\u7871 n g\u7847 n t\u7899 i b\'f3ng c\u7853 u in tr\'ean m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t...\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean r\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, gi\'e3y gi\u7909 a t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i t\u7915  trong gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng, nh\'ecn tr\u7847 n nh\'e0 quen thu\u7897 c m\u7899 i tho\'e1ng b\'ecnh t\u297 nh l\u7841 i, l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ra s\u7913 c chen v\'e0o ch\u7895  nam nh\'e2n \u273 ang ng\u7911  say b\'ean c\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n v\'f4 th\uc0\u7913 c du\u7895 i tay \'f4m c\u7853 u: "L\u7841 i g\u7863 p \'e1c m\u7897 ng?" Tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 r\'f5 r\'e0ng ng\u432 \u7901 i trong ng\u7921 c n\'e0y ch\'ea n\'f3ng kh\'f4ng cho h\u7855 n \'f4m, k\u7871 t qu\u7843  l\'fac s\u7907  h\'e3i l\u7841 i chui v\'e0o, th\u7853 t s\u7921  l\'e0 qua c\u7847 u r\'fat v\'e1n v\u7855 t chanh b\u7887  v\u7887 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong b\uc0\u7909 ng qu\u7903  tr\'e1ch nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n nh\u7883 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 au l\'f2ng, m\u7873 m gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "\u272 \u7915 ng s\u7907 , \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 m\u417  th\'f4i, anh \u7903  \u273 \'e2y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\uc0\u7869  "V\'e2ng" m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, l\u7841 i c\'e0ng \'f4m ch\u7863 t h\u7855 n kh\'f4ng bu\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i cho ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e2y kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  l\'e0 gi\u7845 c m\u417  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 s\u7921  th\u7853 t ch\'ednh c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 tr\u7843 i qua, k\'fd \u7913 c nh\u432  m\u7897 t c\u417 n \'e1c m\u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7845 y n\u259 m tr\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\u7915 a m\u7899 i t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p c\u7845 p ba.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u \u7903  nh\'e0 lo l\u7855 ng ch\u7901  k\u7871 t qu\u7843  thi \u272 \u7841 i H\u7885 c, anh h\u7885  V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh ngh\u7881  h\'e8 tr\u7903  v\u7873  nh\'e0 th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u273 \u7913 ng ng\u7891 i kh\'f4ng y\'ean b\'e8n \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  \u273 \u432 a c\u7853 u \u273 i ch\u417 i gi\u7843 i s\u7847 u, c\u7853 u \u273 \u7905  ph\u7843 i m\u7895 i ng\'e0y \u7903  nh\'e0 th\u7845 p th\u7887 m bu\u7891 n b\u7921 c. Cha m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean nghe v\u7853 y c\u361 ng r\u7845 t \u7911 ng h\u7897 , khuy\u7871 n kh\'edch c\u7853 u n\'ean theo anh h\u7885  ra ngo\'e0i \u273 i ch\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh l\'e0 con trai c\u7911 a b\'e1c Tr\'ec Di\'ean, k\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u361 ng ch\u7881  h\u417 n Tr\'ec Di\'ean ba tu\u7893 i, n\u259 m \u273 \'f3 anh l\'ean n\u259 m t\u432  \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, chuy\'ean ng\'e0nh li\'ean quan \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 a l\'fd. Ngh\u7881  h\'e8 n\u259 m ba tr\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7885 c y\'eau c\u7847 u c\'e1c sinh vi\'ean t\u7841 o nh\'f3m \u273 i kh\u7843 o s\'e1t th\u7921 c \u273 \u7883 a, sau khi khai gi\u7843 ng ph\u7843 i vi\u7871 t b\'e1o c\'e1o, c\'f2n ph\u7843 i di\u7877 n gi\u7843 i. V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh v\u7899 i b\u7841 n g\'e1i L\u432 u V\u361  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\'e0 hai b\u7841 n h\u7885 c c\'f9ng khoa kh\'e1c l\'e0 Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o v\'e0 L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i l\u7853 p th\'e0nh m\u7897 t nh\'f3m b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i l\'e0 \uc0\u273 i th\u7921 c t\u7871  nh\u432 ng th\u7901 i gian v\'e0 \u273 \u7883 a \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  ch\u7885 n, kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c du l\u7883 ch l\'e0 m\u7845 y, n\u7897 p s\u7899 m cho khoa b\'e1o c\'e1o m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n k\u7871  ho\u7841 ch l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, v\u7853 y n\'ean V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh trao \u273 \u7893 i v\u7899 i ba ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7857 ng mu\u7889 n mang em h\u7885  c\u7911 a m\'ecnh theo. D\'f9 sao Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nh\u7887 , c\'e1c v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  sinh ho\u7841 t c\'f3 th\u7875  t\u7921  lo \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. L\u432 u V\u361  tuy l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh nh\u432 ng d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng l\'e0 con g\'e1i, mu\u7889 n \u7903  ph\'f2ng \u273 \u417 n, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f3 th\u7875  \u7903  chung ph\'f2ng v\u7899 i V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 b\uc0\u7885 n h\u7885  tu\u7893 i t\'e1c kh\'f4ng ch\'eanh l\u7879 ch l\u7855 m, ba ng\u432 \u7901 i nghe xong li\u7873 n \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7885 n \u273 i th\u7921 c t\u7871  \u7903  t\u7881 nh Qu\u7843 ng T\'e2y, n\u417 i c\'f3 \u273 \u7883 a h\'ecnh t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, khu v\u7921 c n\'e0y c\'f3 \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i \u273 \u7891 i n\'fai thung l\u117 \u771 ng khe c\u7889 c, c\u361 ng h\'ecnh th\'e0nh nhi\u7873 u d\u7841 ng \u273 \u7883 a h\'ecnh n\'fai \u273 \'e1 v\'f4i, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 i\u7875 m tham quan n\u7893 i ti\u7871 ng l\'e0 n\u417 i c\'f3 phong c\u7843 nh \u273 \u7883 a h\'ecnh \u273 \u7897 c \u273 \'e1o, ho\'e0n to\'e0n l\'e0 m\u7897 t n\u417 i r\u7845 t t\u7889 t \u273 \u7875  \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i ch\u417 i \u7903  Qu\u7843 ng T\'e2y m\u432 \u7901 i ng\'e0y, nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i n\u7893 i danh c\u361 ng \u273 i qua m\u7897 t l\u432 \u7907 t, l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 thu th\u7853 p \u273 \u7911  t\u432  li\u7879 u th\u7921 c t\u7871  d\'f9ng cho b\'e1o c\'e1o, \u273 \u7871 n khi ng\u7891 i t\'e0u h\u7887 a quay v\u7873  t\u7881 nh th\'ec g\u7863 p m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng trung ni\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Lo\uc0\u7841 i t\'e0u h\u7887 a m\'e0u xanh l\u7909 c ki\u7875 u c\u361  n\'e0y b\'e0i tr\'ed m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c b\'e0n nh\u7887  c\'f3 hai gh\u7871  \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n nhau, c\'f3 th\u7875  ng\u7891 i s\'e1u ng\u432 \u7901 i, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng kia \u273 \'fang l\'fac c\'f9ng ng\u7891 i c\'f9ng m\u7897 t ch\u7895  v\u7899 i n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u7903  s\'e1t c\u7917 a s\u7893 , r\u7845 t t\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 b\u7855 t chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 . Sau khi bi\u7871 t m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh \u273 \u7873 u h\u7885 c \u273 \u7883 a l\'fd \'f4ng ta t\u7887  ra r\u7845 t b\u7845 t ng\u7901 , n\'f3i m\'ecnh c\u361 ng l\'e0m nghi\'ean c\u7913 u \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7845 t, b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 ang c\'f4ng t\'e1c \u7903  t\u7881 nh Qu\u7843 ng T\'e2y, bi\u7871 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 ang \u273 i th\u7921 c t\u7871  c\'f2n nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u qu\'ea m\'ecnh, b\u7843 o m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'ecm m\u7897 t n\u417 i c\'f3 t\'ean l\'e0 th\'f4n H\u7891 ng \u272 \u7891 , n\'f3i quanh n\u417 i \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u hang \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \'e1 v\'f4i ch\u432 a b\u7883  khai ph\'e1 hi\u7871 m ai bi\u7871 t, c\u7843 nh s\u7855 c c\'f2n \u273 \u7865 p h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u nh\u7919 ng danh lam n\u7893 i ti\u7871 ng, h\u417 n n\u7919 a l\u7841 i c\'e0ng c\'f3 gi\'e1 tr\u7883  nghi\'ean c\u7913 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a nghe ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng kia n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e2m. V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh v\'e0 L\u432 u V\u361  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n ng\u7855 m phong c\u7843 nh nguy\'ean s\u417 , L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i th\'ec c\'f3 suy ngh\u297  th\u7921 c t\u7871  h\u417 n. H\u7855 n nghe n\'f3i th\'e0nh t\'edch b\'e1o c\'e1o th\u7921 c t\u7871  l\u7847 n n\'e0y s\u7869  \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n c\u417  h\u7897 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m nghi\'ean c\u7913 u sinh, h\u7855 n mu\u7889 n \u7903  l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\u7885 c l\'ean th\u7841 c s\u297  n\'ean mu\u7889 n k\u7871 t qu\u7843  \u273 i th\u7921 c t\u7871  xu\u7845 t s\u7855 c m\u7897 t ch\'fat. L\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c h\u7855 n v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u432  li\u7879 u b\u7885 n h\u7885  thu \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7851 n h\u417 i t\u7847 m th\u432 \u7901 ng, th\u7921 c ra ch\u432 a qu\'e1 h\'e0i l\'f2ng, cho n\'ean sau khi nghe n\'f3i v\u7853 y c\'e0ng ra s\u7913 c th\'fac gi\u7909 c m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7871 n th\'f4n H\u7891 ng \u272 \u7891  kia xem th\u7917  m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, d\'f9 sao c\u361 ng ch\u7881  t\u7889 n th\'eam c\'f9ng l\u7855 m ba b\u7889 n ng\'e0y. B\u7903 i v\'ec k\u7923  th\u7921 c t\u7871  h\'e8 n\'e0y m\'e0 m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881  t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i s\u7899 m, c\'e1ch khai gi\u7843 ng c\'f2n g\u7847 n hai th\'e1ng n\u7919 a, m\u7845 t th\'eam m\u7845 y h\'f4m c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1ng k\u7875  .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y sau khi \u273 i t\'e0u v\u7873 , n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean m\u7841 ng t\'ecm ki\u7871 m v\u7899 i h\u7887 i th\u259 m d\u7885 c \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \'e3 t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4n H\u7891 ng \u272 \u7891 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n qu\'e1n tr\u7885  duy nh\u7845 t trong th\'f4n b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\u7841 i g\u7863 p m\u7897 t thanh ni\'ean t\u7921  x\u432 ng L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n, L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n n\'f3i quanh \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng d\u7877  \u273 i h\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'f4ng d\u7877  t\'ecm, h\u7855 n c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng cho b\u7885 n h\u7885 , \u273 \u432 a b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7919 ng n\u417 i c\'f3 \u273 \u7883 a ch\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 a h\'ecnh \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t kia, m\u7895 i ng\'e0y ch\u7881  c\u7847 n m\u7897 t tr\u259 m \u273 \u7891 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t tr\u259 m \u273 \u7891 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ednh l\'e0 nhi\u234 \u768 u, chia ra m\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7881  m\u7845 t hai m\u432 \u417 i \u273 \u7891 ng, c\'f3 d\'e2n b\u7843 n x\u7913  d\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  gi\u7843 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u phi\u7873 n to\'e1i, m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd. Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'fac \u7845 y nh\u7887  tu\u7893 i nh\u7845 t, cha m\u7865  d\u7863 n d\'f2 ph\u7843 i nghe l\u7901 i anh h\u7885 , kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\u7921  \'fd quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh, v\u7851 n lu\'f4n nh\u432  ch\'e2n sai v\u7863 t \u273 i theo V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'eam trong qu\'e1n tr\u7885 , s\'e1ng h\'f4m sau t\'e1m gi\u7901  L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n \u273 \u7871 n g\u7885 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t l\'ean n\'fai. N\'fai tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 cao nh\u432 ng c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u khe n\'fai y\'ean t\u297 nh, L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n mang theo b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i v\'e0o t\u7915  m\u7897 t khe nh\u7887 , th\u7901 i gian \u273 i r\u7845 t l\'e2u, tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u t\u432  li\u7879 u c\'f3 gi\'e1 tr\u7883 , m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i d\u7915 ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i nh\u7863 t r\u7891 i l\u7841 i ph\u7911 i, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u r\u7845 t ph\u7845 n kh\u7903 i h\u432 ng ph\u7845 n, c\u7843 m gi\'e1c l\u7847 n n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 \u273 i \u273 \'fang n\u417 i r\u7891 i. \u272 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u g\u7847 n ba gi\u7901  L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n d\u7851 n b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t c\u7917 a hang \u273 \'e1 v\'f4i, n\'f3i c\u7843 nh tr\'ed b\'ean trong c\'f2n \u273 \u7897 c \u273 \'e1o h\u417 n, h\u7887 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  c\'f3 mu\u7889 n \u273 i v\'e0o hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 N\uc0\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i k\u7923  th\u7853 t c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 r\u7845 t m\u7879 t, h\u417 n n\u7919 a th\u7901 i gian kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u7899 m, quay v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u361  c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i s\'e1u b\u7843 y gi\u7901  m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7903  l\u7841 i trong th\'f4n. Nh\u432 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  l\u7841 i b\u7883  l\u7901 i L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n mi\'eau t\u7843  c\u7843 nh tr\'ed trong \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \'e1 v\'f4i h\u7845 p d\u7851 n, c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\u7871 u l\u7847 n n\'e0y b\u7887  l\u7905  c\u417  h\u7897 i th\'ec s\u7869  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u7847 n sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ecnh \uc0\u272 \'e0o h\u7887 i L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n trong hang c\'f3 l\u7899 n hay kh\'f4ng, L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n n\'f3i kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 i v\'e0o nh\'ecn qua m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i \u273 i ra. V\'ec v\u7853 y Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o n\'f3i c\u7913  \u273 i v\'e0o xem th\u7917 , t\u7889 i \u273 a n\u7917 a gi\u7901  s\u7869  \u273 i ra, nh\u432  v\u7853 y l\'fac v\u7873  tr\u7901 i s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 t\u7889 i, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng quay v\u7873  th\'f4n qu\'e1 mu\u7897 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7897 ng r\u7845 t t\u7889 i, Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o v\u7899 i V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh \u273 \u7873 u b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n pin, kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7915 a m\u7899 i \u273 i v\'e0o, ngo\'e0i c\u7917 a hang \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 l\u7899 n r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng b\u7883 t k\'edn c\u7917 a \u273 \u7897 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ecnh \uc0\u272 \'e0o h\'f4 to m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n, ph\u7843 i l\'e0m sao b\'e2y gi\u7901 ? Ch\'fang ta l\'e0m sao \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2y?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ai \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i. D\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh \u273 \'e8n ch\u7881  c\'f3 n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7867  tu\u7893 i hai m\u7863 t nh\'ecn nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t l\'e1t sau L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i m\u7899 i ph\'e1 v\u7905  im l\u7863 ng: "... V\u7915 a r\u7891 i h\'ecnh nh\u432  h\u7855 n ta \u273 i cu\u7889 i, kh\'f4ng \u273 i v\'e0o c\'f9ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac ti\uc0\u7871 n v\'e0o khe n\'fai \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n m\u7845 t t\'edn hi\u7879 u, hi\u7879 n t\u7841 i mu\u7889 n c\u7847 u c\u7913 u b\'ean ngo\'e0i l\'e0 kh\'f4ng th\u7875 . Trong l\'f2ng m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng b\u7845 t h\u7843 o nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ai n\'f3i ra. N\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u361 ng th\u7917  \u273 \u7849 y t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 nh\u432 ng v\'f4 \'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ecnh \uc0\u272 \'e0o g\'f5 \u273 \'e8n pin ti\u7871 n l\'ean quan s\'e1t ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh b\u7889 n ph\'eda, \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean chi\u7871 u \u273 \'e8n xu\u7889 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t n\'f3i: "N\u417 i n\'e0y c\'f3 n\u432 \u7899 c, h\u7859 n l\'e0 c\'f3 s\'f4ng ng\u7847 m b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i, h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\'f3 th\u7875  c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng kh\'ed l\u432 u \u273 \u7897 ng, c\'f2n c\'f3 c\u7843  gi\'f3. N\u417 i \u273 \'e2y ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\u7917 a \u273 \u7897 ng n\'e0y, khe n\'fai n\'e0y c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\u7899 n, \u273 \u7897 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng qu\'e1 d\'e0i, ch\'fang ta men theo n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i theo h\u432 \u7899 ng gi\'f3 h\u7859 n l\'e0 s\u7869  t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7917 a ra."\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y ra k\'eau la \u273 \u7849 y t\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 c\u361 ng ch\u7881  ph\'ed s\u7913 c, t\u7845 t c\u7843  m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd v\u7899 i \u273 \u7873  ngh\u7883  c\u7911 a Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o, ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 i d\u7885 c theo \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0o b\'ean trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7897 ng r\u7845 t l\u7841 nh, Tr\'ec Di\'ean m\u7863 c \'e1o kho\'e1c m\u7887 ng nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i l\u7841 nh th\u7845 m v\'e0o x\u432 \u417 ng, kh\'f4ng kh\u7887 i \'f4m ch\u7863 t hai tay. H\u417 n n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u7843 o gi\'e1c hay kh\'f4ng, c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \'e1nh m\u7855 t \u273 ang nh\'ecn m\'ecnh, nh\u432 ng b\u7889 n ph\'eda r\'f5 r\'e0ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i h\u417 n m\u7897 t gi\u7901 , n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u c\'e0ng th\'eam m\u7879 t m\u7887 i, m\'e0 m\u7879 t nh\u7845 t ch\'ednh l\'e0 d\'e0y v\'f2 t\'e2m l\'fd, b\u7885 n h\u7885  ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 o\u7841 n \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f2n bao xa, c\'f2n ph\u7843 i \u273 i bao l\'e2u. \u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u361 ng ch\u7881  c\'f2n \'edt pin. \u272 \u7875  duy tr\'ec ngu\u7891 n s\'e1ng, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u t\u7855 t di \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0 \u273 \'e8n pin, ch\u7881  \u273 \u7875  V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh c\u7847 m \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c soi \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7897 t nhi\'ean b\u7889 n ph\'eda ho\'e0n to\'e0n ch\'ecm v\'e0o b\'f3ng t\u7889 i. \u272 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \'e3 h\u7871 t pin.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh v\u7897 i v\'e0ng m\u7903  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh soi tho\'e1ng qua b\u7889 n ph\'eda, n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u \u7903  \u273 \'e2y, b\'ean ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7897 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7847 m n\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng r\'f5 n\'f4ng s\'e2u, ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\'e3 ba.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n h\u432 \u7899 ng gi\'f3, do d\u7921  kh\'f4ng ch\u7855 c n\'ean \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0o, Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o \u273 \u7913 ng c\u7841 nh anh, im l\u7863 ng n\'e2ng ng\'f3n tay ch\u7881  b\'ean tr\'e1i. N\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u432 \u7899 i s\u7921  d\u7851 n d\u7855 t c\u7911 a V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh \u273 i v\u7873  ph\'eda b\'ean tr\'e1i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i \u273 i sau c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7889 n \u273 ang \u273 i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng, L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ch\u7853 m l\u7841 i hai b\u432 \u7899 c c\u7889  \'fd \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n c\u7841 nh c\u7853 u, h\u7841  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "Ti\u7875 u Tr\'ec, anh h\u7887 i c\u7853 u m\u7897 t chuy\u7879 n, v\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\u7853 u c\'f3 \u273 \u7875  \'fd Tr\'ecnh ca kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  nghe L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i nh\u432  l\u7849 m b\u7849 m \u273 \u7897 c tho\u7841 i: "Nh\u432 ng v\u7915 a r\u7891 i h\'ecnh nh\u432  anh nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng th\u7913  g\'ec r\u417 i v\'e0o n\u432 \u7899 c. L\'fac anh c\u7853 u m\u7903  \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i l\'ean \u273 \'fang l\'fac anh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o b\'f2 ra t\u7915  trong n\u432 \u7899 c, c\'f2n c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i anh n\u7919 a. Nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u ta l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec c\u7843 , qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u432 \u7899 t... Ch\u7859 ng l\u7869  l\'e0 anh nh\'ecn l\u7847 m..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tim Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7853 p b\u7897 p m\u7897 t c\'e1i, nh\u432 ng c\u7853 u v\u7851 n mi\u7877 n c\u432 \u7905 ng c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1p: "L\'fd ca anh \u273 \u7915 ng d\u7885 a ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7919 a, m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n ma qu\u7927  \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883 a ra \u273 \u7875  h\'f9 d\u7885 a ng\u432 \u7901 i ta th\'f4i, nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 anh nh\'ecn l\u7847 m r\u7891 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 n th\'e2n L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng d\'e1m kh\u7859 ng \u273 \u7883 nh, \u273 \'e0nh im l\u7863 ng \u273 i ti\u7871 p, kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng l\'e2u sau m\uc0\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7907 t nghe th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec r\u417 i v\'e0o n\u432 \u7899 c, ti\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 ti\u7871 ng con g\'e1i h\'e9t l\u7899 n, L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i nhanh ch\'f3ng b\u7853 t \u273 \'e8n pin trong tay, c\'f9ng V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh chi\u7871 u \u273 \'e8n v\u7873  h\u432 \u7899 ng ph\'e1t ra \'e2m thanh.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7845 t c\u7843  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y "Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o" \u273 ang ng\'e2m m\'ecnh trong n\u432 \u7899 c, ch\u7881  c\'f3 ph\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u l\u7897  tr\'ean m\u7863 t n\u432 \u7899 c c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 , l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 ang k\'e9o L\u432 u V\u361  xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7847 m n\u432 \u7899 c, h\u417 n n\u7917 a ng\u432 \u7901 i L\u432 u V\u361  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  "h\u7855 n" k\'e9o v\'e0o trong n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh v\u7897 i v\'e0ng n\'e9m t\'fai c\u7911 a m\'ecnh v\u7873  ph\'eda "Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o" kia, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i th\'f2 tay k\'e9o L\u432 u V\u361 , nh\u432 ng s\u7913 c anh ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7883 ch l\u7841 i l\u7921 c \u273 ang k\'e9o L\u432 u V\u361 , ngay c\u7843  anh c\u361 ng s\u7855 p b\u7883  k\'e9o xu\u7889 ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i ch\u7841 y qua h\u7895  tr\u7907  nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n v\'f4 \'edch.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y t\uc0\u7915  trong \u273 \u7847 m n\u432 \u7899 c l\u7841 i c\'f3 r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u c\'e1nh tay tr\u7855 ng h\u7871 u nh\'f4 l\'ean, du\u7895 i ra v\u7899 i t\u7899 i ba ng\u432 \u7901 i mu\u7889 n k\'e9o b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\'e0o n\u432 \u7899 c. L\u432 u V\u361  \u273 \'e3 ch\u7881  c\'f2n ph\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u l\u7897  tr\'ean m\u7863 t n\u432 \u7899 c, th\u7845 y th\u7871  kh\'f3c l\u7899 n: "V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh anh ch\u7841 y \u273 i, anh mau ch\u7841 y \u273 i, n\u417 i n\'e0y r\u7845 t t\'e0 m\'f4n, m\u7863 c k\u7879  em, m\u7863 c k\u7879  em, anh mau ch\u7841 y \u273 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fd Phong Kh\uc0\u7843 i kh\u7869  c\u7855 n m\'f4i, bu\'f4ng l\u7887 ng tay \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean, m\'e0 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh m\u7855 t th\u7845 y \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p b\u7883  nh\u7919 ng c\'e1nh tay tr\u7855 ng h\u7871 u \u432 \u7899 t s\u361 ng v\u7899 i t\u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y nh\u7919 ng c\'e1nh tay kia \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, hang \u273 \u7897 ng gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  s\u7889 ng d\u7853 y, t\u7915  trong ra ngo\'e0i vang l\'ean t\u7847 ng t\u7847 ng l\u7899 p l\u7899 p v\'f4 s\u7889  \'e2m thanh y\u7871 u \u7899 t r\u7845 t nh\u7887  r\u7891 i l\u7841 i th\u7843 m thi\u7871 t ch\'f3i tai, ch\u7891 ng ch\'e9o t\'e1i di\u7877 n m\u7897 t c\'e2u, k\u7875  c\u7843  "Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o" ch\u7881  l\u7897  ra m\u7897 t c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u c\u361 ng ng\u7885  ngu\u7853 y m\'f4i, tr\'ean m\u7863 t hi\u7879 n l\'ean v\u7867  s\u7907  h\'e3i nh\u432  ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i l\u7849 m b\u7849 m \'e2m ti\u7871 t \u273 \u7891 ng d\u7841 ng: "Th\u7847 n s\u7855 p t\u7881 nh... Th\u7847 n s\u7855 p t\u7881 nh..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7915 a d\u7883 p nh\u7919 ng th\u7913  n\'e0y ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, Tr\'ec Di\'ean k\'e9o anh m\'ecnh tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i ph\u7841 m vi nh\u7919 ng c\'e1nh tay kia, nh\u432 ng L\u432 u V\u361  \u273 \'e3 ho\'e0n to\'e0n b\u7883  k\'e9o v\'e0o \u273 \'e1y n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 ang ng\'e2y ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\'ecn m\u7863 t n\u432 \u7899 c, nh\u7919 ng c\'e1nh tay l\u7841 i c\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng, k\'e9o d\'e0i ra c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n t\u7899 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i, L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i h\'f4 to m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng "Ch\u7841 y mau!" r\u7891 i ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u361 ng k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng k\'e9o V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh l\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 o ch\u7841 y theo.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau khi ch\uc0\u7841 y c\'e1ch xa \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \u273 o\u7841 n, L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i \u7903  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, ng\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u nh\'ecn hai ng\u432 \u7901 i: "C\u7853 u n\'f3i xem ch\'fang ta c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7841 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ra ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong m\uc0\u7855 t L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i l\u7897  ra s\u7921  tuy\u7879 t v\u7885 ng kh\'f4n c\'f9ng: "T\'f4i nh\u7899  ra v\u7915 a r\u7891 i ch\'ednh h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng cho ch\'fang ta m\'e0."\cb1 \
