\cf2 \cb3 Nghe nh\uc0\u7919 ng l\u7901 i n\'e0y c\u7911 a L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i, l\u7841 i nh\u7899  l\u7841 i t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh l\'fac \u7845 y, Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh \u273 \u7873 u ng\'e2y ng\u7849 n c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i, trong l\'fac nh\u7845 t th\u7901 i ti\u7871 n tho\'e1i l\u432 \u7905 ng nan.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7841 y v\u7873  h\u432 \u7899 ng c\u361 , tr\u7903  l\u7841 i \u273 \u7847 m n\u432 \u7899 c qu\u7927  d\u7883  th\u7853 t v\u7845 t v\u7843  m\u7899 i tho\'e1t ra \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kia, ba ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n; ti\u7871 n v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng ai bi\u7871 t ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 ang \u273 \u7907 i h\u7885 , c\'f2n c\'f3 th\u7875  tr\u7903  ra hay kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh v\u7851 n ch\u432 a tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i kinh s\u7907  v\'e0 \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n m\u7845 t \u273 i L\u432 u V\u361 , \u273 \u7913 ng t\u7841 i ch\u7895  d\'f9ng \u273 \'e8n pin chi\u7871 u s\'e1ng con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng b\u7885 n h\u7885  v\u7915 a ch\u7841 y ra, m\u417  h\u7891  tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y m\u7897 t th\'e2n \u7843 nh \u432 \u7899 t s\u361 ng l\u7843 o \u273 \u7843 o l\'ea l\u7871 t v\u7873  ph\'eda b\u7885 n h\u7885 , nh\'ecn d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, v\u7853 y m\'e0 ch\'ednh l\'e0 "Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o" !\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\'e0 L\'fd Phong Kh\uc0\u7843 i l\'fac n\'e0y c\u361 ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y th\'e2n \u7843 nh kia, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c trong m\u7855 t nhau s\u7921  s\u7907  h\'e3i kh\'f3 n\'e9n.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y kh\'f4ng th\uc0\u7875  suy ngh\u297  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh kh\u7869  qu\'e1t m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng: "\u272 i mau!" r\u7891 i d\u7851 n \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 i ch\u7841 y qua hai l\u7889 i r\u7869 , b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t hang \u273 \u7897 ng t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i tr\u7889 ng tr\u7843 i, xem ch\u7915 ng \u273 \'e3 b\u7887  r\u417 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7913  kia, ba ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i th\u7903  d\u7889 c ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, th\u7845 y L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i cau m\'e0y \u273 ang xem camera trong tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\'ean m\'f4n nh\uc0\u432  L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn ra c\u7845 u t\u7841 o n\u7897 i b\u7897  v\'e0 v\'e1ch \u273 \'e1 trong \u273 \u7897 ng n\'e0y \u273 \u7873 u t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t, L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i c\'e0ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng b\u7887  qua, tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o v\'e0 L\u432 u V\u361  g\u7863 p chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng may, tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i h\u7855 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n c\u7847 m camera ch\u7909 p l\u7841 i b\u7889 n v\'e1ch hang.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay L\'fd Phong Kh\uc0\u7843 i run b\u7847 n b\u7853 t, n\u7871 u kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\'f2n d\'e2y n\u7889 i camera \u273 eo tr\'ean c\u7893 , c\'f3 l\u7869  h\u7855 n \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m r\u417 i m\'e1y xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f9ng V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7841 i g\u7847 n nh\'ecn, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y c\'e1c b\u7913 c \u7843 nh d\u432 \u7899 i t\'e1c d\u7909 ng c\u7911 a \u273 \'e8n flash c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y m\u7895 i m\u7863 t tr\'ean v\'e1ch hang \u273 \u7873 u chi\u7871 u ra m\u7897 t v\'e0i b\'f3ng d\'e1ng h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0u \u273 en m\u417  m\u417  h\u7891  h\u7891 , m\'e0 nh\u7919 ng c\'e1i b\'f3ng n\'e0y v\u7915 a r\u7891 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  d\'f9ng m\u7855 t th\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7873  ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh nu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t, th\'f2 tay t\u7855 t camera: "\u272 \u7915 ng xem n\u7919 a, mau ch\u7841 y ti\u7871 p th\'f4i." K\u7923  th\u7853 t tr\u7843 i qua c\'e1i ch\u7871 t c\u7911 a L\u432 u V\u361  v\'e0 Tr\'ecnh \u272 \'e0o, \u273 i\u7875 m t\'e0 m\'f4n trong \u273 \u7897 ng n\'e0y qu\u7843  th\u7921 c \u273 \'e3 r\'f5 r\'e0ng, c\'f3 s\u7907  h\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \'edch g\'ec, g\u7855 ng s\u7913 c b\u7887  ch\u7841 y m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng s\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'eda tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7897 ng xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \'e1nh s\'e1ng kh\'f4ng r\'f5, nh\'ecn k\u7929  m\u7899 i ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n l\'e0 ch\'f3p nham th\u7841 ch tr\'ean v\'e1ch hang ph\'e1t ra tia s\'e1ng. N\u7871 u \u273 \u7893 i t\'ecnh c\u7843 nh l\'fac n\'e0y v\'e0o l\'fac kh\'e1c, Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7845 t \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7869  th\'e1n ph\u7909 c s\u7921  k\u7923  di\u7879 u c\u7911 a t\u7841 o h\'f3a, c\u7853 u ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y n\u417 i n\'e0o c\'f3 nham th\u7841 ch ph\'e1t ra m\'e0u v\'e0ng m\u7901  \u7843 o nh\u432  v\u7853 y, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \'e1nh l\u7917 a b\u7883  che trong l\u7891 ng \u273 \'e8n m\'e0u tro. Nh\u432 ng \'e1nh s\'e1ng \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean xu\u7845 t hi\u7879 n \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0y ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7875  mang cho b\u7885 n h\u7885  s\u7921  xoa d\u7883 u ng\u7855 n ng\u7911 i, ngay sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7853 p t\u7913 c khi\u7871 n h\u7885  c\'e0ng th\'eam s\u7907  h\'e3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7903 i v\'ec d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh s\'e1ng l\u417 \u768  m\u417 \u768  kia c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y r\'f5 tr\'ean v\'e1ch \u273 \'e1 hai b\'ean gi\u259 ng \u273 \u7847 y nh\u7919 ng chi\u7871 c b\'f3ng m\'e0u \u273 en, t\u7921 a nh\u432  h\'ecnh d\'e1ng m\u417  h\u7891  trong \u7843 nh L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i ch\u7909 p. Ch\u7895  g\u7847 n c\'f3 th\u7875  th\u7845 y l\'e0 b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i k\'e9o d\'e0i, xa h\u417 n ch\u7881  l\'e0 h\'ecnh ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng r\'f5.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh k\u7883 p ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean, qu\'e1t: "\u272 i mau, ch\'fang bi\u7871 t c\u7917  \u273 \'f4\u803 ng."\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh n\'f3i kh\'f4ng sai. Ch\u7881  nh\'ecn b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng s\u7869  r\u7845 t kh\'f3 ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n v\'ec nh\u7919 ng chi\u7871 c "B\'f3ng" kia di chuy\u7875 n c\u7921 c k\u7923  nh\u7887 , m\u7855 t th\u432 \u7901 ng h\u7847 u nh\u432  kh\'f4ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n ra, nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u nh\u432  ch\'fa \'fd quan s\'e1t kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch gi\u7919 a nh\u7919 ng chi\u7871 c b\'f3ng kia v\u7899 i b\'f3ng ba ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7885 n h\u7885 , c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u7853 n ra kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch hai b\'ean c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng g\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ba ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u li\u7873 u m\u7841 ng ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c, ai c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian li\u7871 c v\u7873  sau, nh\u7919 ng chi\u7871 c b\'f3ng kia l\u7841 i nh\u432  b\u7883  kinh \u273 \u7897 ng, \u273 \u7897 ng t\'e1c tr\u7903  n\'ean c\u7921 c k\u7923  nhanh. \u272 \u7897 t nhi\'ean Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m gi\'e1c m\'ecnh b\u7883  m\u7897 t b\'e0n l\u7841 nh bu\u7889 t t\'f3m l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ch\u7841 y n\u7893 i, V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh v\u7851 n lu\'f4n l\u432 u \'fd em h\u7885  m\'ecnh c\u361 ng ng\u7915 ng l\u7841 i theo, quay \u273 \u7847 u h\u7887 i: "Ti\u7875 u Di\'ean, sao th\u7871 ?"\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i c\'f9ng anh, tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y g\u432 \u417 ng m\u7863 t L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i th\u7889 ng kh\u7893  nh\'ecn m\'ecnh, h\u7855 n n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t c\u7893  tay Tr\'ec Di\'ean: "\u272 \u7915 ng b\u7887  l\u7841 i anh, c\u7913 u anh v\u7899 i, xin c\u7853 u c\u7913 u anh v\u7899 i."\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7847 m m\u7855 t Tr\'ec Di\'ean chuy\u7875 n d\u7901 i xu\u7889 ng m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, v\'f4 s\u7889  b\'f3ng \u273 en \u273 \'e3 bao tr\'f9m l\'ean b\'f3ng c\u7911 a L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i, n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y b\'f3ng c\u7911 a h\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e0 b\'f3ng L\'fd Phong Kh\uc0\u7843 i v\u7853 y m\'e0 c\u361 ng b\u259 \u769 t \u273 \u226 \u768 u chuy\'ea\u777 n \u273 \'f4\u803 ng, th\u7917  th\u259 m d\'f2 t\u7899 i b\'f3ng c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \u7847 u Tr\'ec Di\'ean hi\u7879 n l\'ean m\u7897 t \'fd ngh\u297 , L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh th\u7913  gi\u7889 ng nh\u7919 ng b\'f3ng \u273 en kia. Trong l\'f2ng c\u7853 u ho\u7843 ng lo\u7841 n, tay l\u7841 i b\u7883  L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i l\'f4i k\'e9o kh\'f4ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7897 ng, c\u7853 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\'ecn th\u432  sinh l\'fac n\'e0y l\'e0m sao l\u7841 i c\'f3 s\u7913 c l\u7921 c l\u7899 n \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432 ng th\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m tay c\u7911 a b\'f3ng L\'fd Phong Kh\u7843 i v\u7915 a \u273 \u7909 ng ph\u7843 i b\'f3ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean, n\'f3 l\u7841 i nh\u432  b\u7883  b\u7887 ng, v\u7897 i v\'e0ng r\u7909 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y tay L\'fd Phong Kh\uc0\u7843 i c\u361 ng b\u7883  c\u7853 u gi\'e3y tho\'e1t ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh b\u7855 t chu\u7849 n c\u417  h\u7897 i, k\'e9o c\u7853 u ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ch\u7841 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng d\'e1m d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t m\u7897 t m\u7921 c c\u7855 m \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7841 y v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong tr\'ed nh\uc0\u7899  Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\u7881  c\'f2n l\u7841 i ti\u7871 ng tim \u273 \u7853 p c\u7921 c nhanh c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, ti\u7871 ng b\u432 \u7899 c ch\'e2n d\u7891 n d\u7853 p c\u7911 a hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng ti\u7871 ng th\'ec th\'e0o khe kh\u7869  li\'ean mi\'ean kh\'f4ng d\u7913 t: "Th\u7847 n s\u7855 p t\u7881 nh... Th\u7847 n s\u7855 p t\u7881 nh..."\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai anh em may m\uc0\u7855 n tr\'e1nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u c\'e1nh tay tr\u7855 ng nh\u7907 t, nh\u7919 ng b\'f3ng \u273 en qu\u7927  qu\'e1i t\u432 \u417 ng t\u7921 , cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ph\'e1t hi\u7879 n m\u7897 t c\u7917 a hang th\'f4ng ra b\'ean ngo\'e0i. Nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7871 n khi c\'f2n c\'e1ch c\u7917 a hang m\u432 \u7901 i m\'e9t, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7883  m\u7897 t th\u7913  m\'e1u th\u7883 t l\u7851 n l\u7897 n gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  x\'e1c s\u7889 ng c\u7843 n l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i ra s\u7913 c ch\u7841 y v\'e0i b\u432 \u7899 c, m\u7855 t th\u7845 y \u273 \'e3 s\u7855 p c\'f3 th\u7875  ch\u7841 y ra, \u273 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y c\u7917 a hang b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7845 n \u273 \u7897 ng, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u \u273 \'e1 v\u7909 n r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng. M\'e0 khi \u273 \'f3 th\u7913  kia c\u7855 n l\'ean vai V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh, t\'f3m ch\u7863 t kh\'f4ng cho anh \u273 i. V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh nh\'ecn c\u7917 a hang ch\u7881  c\'f2n c\'e1ch m\u7897 t b\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7855 n, l\u7841 i nh\'ecn em h\u7885 , cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng ch\u7911  \u273 \u7897 ng quay ng\u432 \u7901 i x\'f4ng v\u7873  ph\'eda x\'e1c s\u7889 ng, \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \u273 \u7849 y Tr\'ec Di\'ean kh\u7887 i c\u7917 a hang, qu\'e1t: "Ch\u7841 y mau!"\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngay khi Tr\'ec Di\'ean v\uc0\u7915 a b\u7883  \u273 \u7849 y ra, \u273 \u7911  lo\u7841 i \u273 \'e1 l\u7899 n nh\u7887  l\u259 n xu\u7889 ng ho\'e0n to\'e0n ch\u7863 n k\'edn c\u7917 a hang c\u7853 u v\u7915 a tho\'e1t kh\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi \uc0\u273 \'f3 b\'ean ngo\'e0i tr\u7901 i \u273 \'e3 t\u7843 ng s\'e1ng, b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 b\u7883  nh\u7889 t trong hang c\u7843  \u273 \'eam.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean l\'e0m k\'fd hi\uc0\u7879 u l\'ean c\u7917 a hang r\u7891 i men theo \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i, \u273 i ch\u7915 ng m\u432 \u7901 i ph\'fat th\'ec g\u7863 p nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang \u273 i t\'ecm b\u7885 n h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\'ec ra \'f4ng ch\uc0\u7911  qu\'e1n tr\u7885  bi\u7871 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng l\'ean n\'fai, \u273 \'e3 khuya nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ch\u432 a tr\u7903  v\u7873 , bi\u7871 t b\u7885 n h\u7885  kh\'f4ng mang \u273 \u7911  trang b\u7883 , c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd \u273 \u7883 nh qua \u273 \'eam b\'ean ngo\'e0i n\'ean s\u7907  l\'e0 h\u7885  \u273 \'e3 g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n kh\'f4ng may, b\u7903 i v\u7853 y \u273 \'e3 b\'e1o c\u7843 nh s\'e1t, r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u thanh ni\'ean trai tr\'e1ng trong th\'f4n sau khi nghe v\u7853 y c\u361 ng \u273 i theo gi\'fap t\'ecm ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\uc0\u7851 n m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i quay l\u7841 i c\u7917 a hang kia, nh\u432 ng b\u7845 t lu\u7853 n t\'ecm th\u7871  n\'e0o c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y, c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\'fd hi\u7879 u m\'ecnh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1nh d\u7845 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 a v\u7873 , ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'e2n c\u7911 a c\u7853 u c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 v\u7897 i v\'e0ng t\u7899 i, c\u7853 u k\u7875  l\u7841 i m\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n cho m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i nghe, k\u7875  l\u7841 i hang \u273 \u7897 ng qu\'e1i \u273 \u7843 n kia, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ai tin l\u7901 i c\u7853 u n\'f3i, ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'f4n H\u7891 ng \u272 \u7891  c\u361 ng nhao nhao t\u7887  v\u7867  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n. Ngay c\u7843  \'f4ng ch\u7911  qu\'e1n tr\u7885  c\u361 ng n\'f3i ch\u432 a t\u7915 ng th\u7845 y L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n "S\'e1ng s\u7899 m \u273 \u7871 n g\u7885 i b\u7885 n h\u7885  xu\u7845 t ph\'e1t" trong l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean, ch\u7881  th\u7845 y n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 eo balo r\u7901 i \u273 i, \'f4ng nh\u7899  r\'f5 m\'ecnh c\'f2n h\u7887 i V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh khi n\'e0o th\'ec quay v\u7873 , V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh \u273 \'e1p bu\u7893 i t\u7889 i n\u259 m s\'e1u gi\u7901  s\u7869  tr\u7903  l\u7841 i, l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng h\u7873  c\'f3 \u7845 n t\u432 \u7907 ng g\'ec v\u7873  L\u7909 c Thu\u7853 n v\u7851 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\'f9ng m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\u259 n c\u7913  v\'e0o l\u7901 i mi\'eau t\u7843  c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean nh\u7853 n \u273 \u7883 nh s\u7921  ki\u7879 n n\'e0y th\'e0nh "B\u7889 n sinh vi\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c XX \u273 i kh\u7843 o s\'e1t th\u7921 c t\u7871  b\u7845 t h\u7841 nh g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i n\'fai s\u7909 p m\'e0 l\'e2m n\u7841 n". Nh\u7919 ng l\u7901 i "\u258 n n\'f3i lung tung" c\u7911 a Tr\'ec Di\'ean b\u7883  coi l\'e0 do ch\u7913 ng ki\u7871 n tai n\u7841 n m\'e0 sinh ra k\'fd \u7913 c h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n, b\u7883  cho l\'e0 m\u7897 t lo\u7841 i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  t\'e2m l\'fd sinh ra do b\u7843 n th\'e2n g\u7863 p n\u7841 n. Sau khi c\u7853 u v\u7873  nh\'e0, cha m\u7865  Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\'f2n d\u7851 n c\u7853 u \u273 i g\u7863 p b\'e1c s\u297  t\'e2m l\'fd m\u7897 t th\'e1ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i tin l\u7901 i Tr\'ec Di\'ean. Ng\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7913 u v\u7873  th\'f4n H\u7891 ng \u272 \u7891  \u273 \'f3, c\u7853 u cu\u7889 ng cu\u7891 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i chuy\u7879 n x\u7843 y ra trong \u273 \u7897 ng, c\u7847 u xin b\u7885 n h\u7885  \u273 i c\u7913 u anh h\u7885 , tuy r\u7857 ng ch\'ednh c\u7853 u c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t hy v\u7885 ng c\u7913 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c V\u432 \u417 ng Th\u7883 nh \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1 xa v\u7901 i. Tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'f3 \u273 o\'e0n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i t\'ecm c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 c\'f9ng c\u7853 u \u273 i v\'e0o khe n\'fai m\u7897 t l\u7847 n, ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng t\'ecm th\u7845 y s\u417 n \u273 \u7897 ng c\u7853 u mi\'eau t\u7843 , m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y c\u7853 u \u273 \'e3 ch\u7883 u k\'edch th\'edch, thay nhau khuy\'ean c\u7853 u ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i cho kh\u7887 e, nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ai tin c\'e2u chuy\u7879 n k\u7923  l\u7841  c\u7911 a c\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t b\'e0 c\u7909  \u7903  c\u7917 a th\'f4n b\u7883  g\u7885 i l\'e0 b\'e0 l\'e3o \u273 i\'ean sau khi m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i t\u7843 n \u273 i l\u7863 ng l\u7869  k\'e9o c\u7853 u l\u7841 i, nh\u7887  gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i: "C\'e1c ng\u432 \u7901 i g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i ma c\u7885 p v\u7891  r\u7891 i, n\u417 i n\'e0y c\'f3 ma c\u7885 p v\u7891  b\u7855 t ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7889 ng cho t\'e0 ma tr\'ean n\'fai \u259 n \u273 \u7845 y."\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\'f2n mu\uc0\u7889 n h\u7887 i th\'eam nh\u432 ng b\'e0 c\u7909  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a, xua xua tay r\u7891 i \u273 i v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 a v\u7873  nh\'e0, tu\u7847 n t\u7921  m\'e0 l\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c, t\u7889 t nghi\u7879 p, \u273 i l\'e0m, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  chuy\u7879 n anh h\u7885  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n, ngo\u7841 i tr\u7915  khi gia \u273 \'ecnh t\u7909  h\u7885 p b\'e1c g\'e1i v\'e0 b\'e1c trai nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7853 u s\u7869  lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng t\u7921  ch\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 l\u7897  ra n\'e9t bi th\u432 \u417 ng, t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c. Kho\u7843 ng th\u7901 i gian ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n tr\u7883  li\u7879 u t\'e2m l\'fd kia c\u7853 u th\u7853 m ch\'ed c\u361 ng t\u7915 ng ngh\u297  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u273 \'fang nh\u432  l\u7901 i b\'e1c s\u297  n\'f3i hay kh\'f4ng, r\u7857 ng nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c m\'e0 b\u7843 n th\'e2n cho r\u7857 ng l\'e0 "K\'fd \u7913 c" kia th\u7853 t ra \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 gi\u7843 , l\'e0 m\'ecnh t\u432 \u7903 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng ra, anh h\u7885  l\'e0 do g\u7863 p ph\u7843 i n\'fai s\u7909 p m\'e0 ch\u7871 t, ch\'ednh m\'ecnh may m\u7855 n tho\'e1t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ki\u7871 p nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  ti\u7871 p nh\u7853 n s\u7921  th\u7853 t n\'e0y n\'ean ti\u7873 m th\u7913 c t\u7921  t\u7841 o ra c\'e2u chuy\u7879 n qu\u7927  d\u7883  nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7871  nh\u432 ng nh\u7919 ng chi ti\u7871 t qu\'e1 m\u7913 c ch\'e2n th\u7853 t \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7915 ng nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  c\u7853 u t\u7845 t c\u7843  \u273 \u7873 u l\'e0 s\u7921  th\u7853 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7853 m ch\'ed d\'f9 \u273 \'e3 qua nhi\u7873 u n\u259 m nh\u432  v\u7853 y, nh\u7919 ng chuy\u7879 n x\u7843 y ra \u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3 v\u7851 n th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean t\'e1i hi\u7879 n trong m\u417 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean sau khi t\uc0\u7881 nh l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i s\u7869  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y nh\u432  lo\'e1ng tho\'e1ng nghe th\u7845 y \'e2m thanh qu\u7927  qu\'e1i kh\'f4ng r\'f5 kia, lu\'f4n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c b\u7889 n v\'e1ch t\u432 \u7901 ng ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  d\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  c\u361 ng in r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u b\'f3ng ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0u \u273 en.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7853 u c\'e0ng ngh\u297  c\'e0ng s\u7907 , \'f4m nam nh\'e2n b\'ean c\u7841 nh, nh\u432  th\'fa nh\u7887  b\u7883  ch\u7845 n kinh kh\u7869  h\'f4n m\'e1 h\'f4n m\'f4i \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nam nh\'e2n trong b\'f3ng \uc0\u273 \'eam n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i: "C\u7909 c c\u432 ng, \u273 \u7915 ng nh\'e1o n\u7919 a, ng\'e0y mai c\'f2n ph\u7843 i \u273 i l\'e0m."\cb1 \
\cb3 "Em m\uc0\u7863 c k\u7879 ," Tr\'ec Di\'ean d\u7913 t kho\'e1t tr\u7903  m\'ecnh \'e1p l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i nam nh\'e2n, "Ngh\'eanh Chi, c\'f9ng em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng, em s\u7907  l\u7855 m, kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c."\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y nam nh\'e2n kh\'f4ng l\u7853 p t\u7913 c \u273 \'e1p l\u7841 i, gi\u7885 ng c\u7853 u c\'e0ng th\'eam t\u7911 i th\'e2n: "Em kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7889  \'fd chi\'eau anh, em th\u7853 t s\u7921  s\u7907  l\u7855 m." M\u7895 i l\u7847 n m\u417  th\u7845 y hang \u273 \u7897 ng n\u259 m \u273 \'f3, sau khi t\u7881 nh l\u7841 i \u273 \u7873 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y x\u432 \u417 ng c\u7889 t l\u7841 nh l\u7869 o.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 "\uc0\u272 \'e3 l\u7899 n bao nhi\'eau r\u7891 i, ch\u7881  m\u7897 t gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng th\'f4i m\'e0 s\u7907  th\'e0nh th\u7871  n\'e0y." Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi th\'f2 tay m\u7903  \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7847 u gi\u432 \u7901 ng, \u273 em ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau tr\u7903  m\'ecnh \'e1p d\u432 \u7899 i th\'e2n h\'f4n c\u7853 u, "Nh\u432 ng em \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i anh c\'f9ng em, v\u7853 y \u273 \'eam nay \u273 \u7915 ng ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n vi\u7879 c ng\u7911  n\u7919 a, l\u7841 i c\'e0ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7893 i \'fd." D\'f9 n\'f3i v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng n\u7871 u \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean nu\u7889 t l\u7901 i nh\'e1o k\'eau bu\u7891 n ng\u7911 , h\u7855 n c\u361 ng s\u7869  kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\'e0m g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i \u273 i\u7875 m h\u7855 n m\u7899 i t\'ecm \u273 \u432 \u7907 c A Di\'ean \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng \u7847 m \u297  d\'ednh ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y, s\u7907  h\'e3i c\u361 ng s\u7869  t\u7921  m\'ecnh ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng. Nh\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\u7841 i \u7927  l\u7841 i v\'e0o h\u7855 n, n\'f3i tr\u7855 ng ra l\'e0 do b\u7843 n th\'e2n h\u7855 n c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u m\'e0 ra, ch\u7859 ng th\u7875  \u273 \u7893  l\u7895 i l\'ean \u273 \u7847 u ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean th\'edch c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\'f9ng Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi ch\u7863 t ch\u7869  t\u432 \u417 ng li\'ean, khi \u273 \'f3 c\u7853 u c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t an t\'e2m, gi\u7889 ng nh\u432  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7889 i ph\u432 \u417 ng b\u7843 o v\u7879  an to\'e0n, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'e1ng s\u7907 . L\'fac n\'e0y Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi s\u7861 n l\'f2ng c\'f9ng c\u7853 u c\u7853 u r\u7845 t vui, \u273 \u432 \u417 ng nhi\'ean s\u7869  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7893 i \'fd, nghe v\u7853 y kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u, hai tay \'f4m l\'ean c\u7893  Di\u7879 p Ngh\'eanh Chi.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i th\u7921 c s\u7921  d\'e2y d\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n h\u7915 ng \u273 \'f4ng, Tr\'ec Di\'ean c\u7843 m th\u7845 y m\u7879 t m\u7887 i, trong l\'fac \'fd th\u7913 c m\'f4ng lung s\u7855 p ch\'ecm v\'e0o gi\u7845 c ng\u7911 , c\u7853 u nghe \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'ean g\u7889 i \'f4m c\u7853 u ph\'e1t ra m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\'e0i th\u7887 a m\'e3n, ngay sau \u273 \'f3 c\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'e1n m\'f4i l\'ean v\u7883  tr\'ed tim c\u7853 u, nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng h\'f4n h\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\'ec Di\'ean ch\uc0\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y huy\u7871 t to\'e0n th\'e2n m\u7841 ch run l\'ean, t\u7915  tr\'e1i tim d\'e2ng l\'ean m\u7897 t h\u7891 i rung \u273 \u7897 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec sao.\cb1 \
